Frances Mao & Fan Wang BBC News Ubushinwa bugiye kuvanaho ‘quarantaine’ [ingingo yo kugumiza umuntu ukwa wenyene] ku ngenzi, ikaba ari yo ntambwe ya nyuma yo kuva kuri poritike ya Covid-zero ico gihugu cari kigize igihe kigenderako
 Inyuma y’imyaka hafi itatu imbibe zugaye, ibi bizotuma igihugu gisubira kwugururwa ku bafise visa z’akazi canke z’amashure, canke abagiye kuramutsa imiryango
 Ariko ivyo bishitse mu gihe Ubushinwa buhanganye n’ikwirakwira rishasha ry’umugera mu gihe izo ngingo zariko ziravanwaho
 Amakuru avuga ko ibitaro vyarengewe n’abarwaye, abageze mu za bukuru nabo bariko barapfa ku bwinshi
 Ibitigiri vy’ukuri – vy’abandura n’abapfa ku munsi ku munsi – ubu ntibizwi kuko abategetsi bahagaritse gushira ahabona ibiharuro bijanye na Covid
 Ku ndwi iheze, ubutegetsi bw’Ubushinwa bwari bwamenyesheje hafi abandura bashasha 4
000 buri munsi n’abapfa bake
 Ku wa Mungu, bavuze ko bagiye guhagarika gushira ahabona ivyo biharuro
 Ariko ikigo co mu Bwongereza kibikurikirana, Airfinity, cagereranije ko mu Bushinwa  handura abantu bashasha barenga umuriyoni hagapfa 5
000 buri munsi, ku bw’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru  Reuters
 Ubushinwa nico gihugu ca nyuma ca rutura mu butunzi gifashe inzira yo “kubana na Covid”  inyuma y’imyaka itatu ya guma mu rugo, kwugara imbibe n’itegeko ryo kuja muri “quarantaine” ku bantu batowe umugera wa Covid canke abagize aho bahurira na bo
 Poritike ya Covid zero yarahungabanije ubutunzi, abanyagihugu nabo bararambwirwa n’ingingo zibabuza ukwishira no kwizana hamwe n’ibipimo vya buri igihe
 Ukurengerwa n’izo ngingo vyararushe bishika ku myiyerekano itamenyerewe muri ico gihugu yo kwiyamiriza prezida Xi Jinping muri Munyonyo (ukwezi kwa 11), ivyatumye abategetsi batezura ingingo za Covid mu mayinga yakurikiye
 Imbibe zugaye niyo nzitizi ya nyuma yari igisigaye
 Kuva muri Ntwarante mu 2020, uwari we wese yinjira mu Bushinwa yategerezwa gushika ashirwa muri quarantaine mu kibanza ca reta – mu kiringo gishika ku ndwi zitatu icarimwe
 Ico ubu vuba caragabanuwe gishirwa ku minsi itanu
 Ariko ku wa mbere, inama y‘igihugu ijejwe amagara yamenyesheje ko Covid igiye kumanurwa igashirwa ku rugero rwa Class B kuva ku wa 8 Nzero
 Ivyo bisigura ko quarantaine izoca ivaho -n’ubwo abavuye hanze bagiye muri ico gihugu bazotegerezwa kugirisha igipimo ca PCR – kandi ko n’igitigiri ntarengwa c’indege zinjira mu Bushinwa ku munsi naco kigiye kuhava
 Abategetsi bavuze kandi bazokworosha ibijanye no gusaba visa ku banyamahanga bifuza kuja mu Bushinwa kwiga, gukora canke kuramutsa umuryango canke kuja kubana nawo
 Ntibiramenyekana niba harimwo na visa ku ngenzi (tourist visa), ariko abategetsi bavuze ko hagiye kuzoba gahunda y’ifatiro ku bwato mpuzamakungu bw’ingenzi
 Ayo mategeko mashasha yakiriwe neza cane n’Abashinwa benshi ubu bagiye gusubira kuja mu makungu
 Kompanyi ya mbere itunganya ingendo kuri internet yamenyesheje ko ibitigiri vy’abayishorera vyaduze cane mu masaha make  izo ngingo zimaze gutangazwa
 Ariko hari n’abandi berekanye agashavu k’ingene ukwo kwidegenvya kuja giturumbuka inyuma y’imyaka y’igenzurwa ritabujije ko abantu baguma bandura
 Abandi bashikirije impungenge ku mbuga hwaniro kuri uko kwugurura imbibe mu gihe abandura Covid basubiye kwiyongera cane mu Bushinwa
 Bumwe mu butumwa bwakunzwe cane kuri Weibo bwagize buti : “Kuki tutari kurindira ko uwu mupfunda ubanza gucureha imbere y’uko twugurura? Abakozi bo kwa muganga basanzwe bamaze kuruha, hanyuma abageze mu za bukuru ntibazorusimba kabiri mu kwezi kumwe”
 Ababa mu bisagara nka Beijing na Shanghai, ubu birangwamwo ubukonje bwinshi, bavuga ko baheranywe n’imiti y’ibicurane kandi bakeneye ubufasha bwo kwa muganga ku babo barwaye
 Hari impungenge ko hari impfu nyinshi zitamenyekana kuko ibibanza vyo guturiramwo abapfuye vyarengewe
 Ku wa mbere, prezida Xi yagize ico avuga ubwa mbere kuri izo mpinduka, asaba abategetsi gukora “ibishoboka” kugira  ubuzima burokorwe
 Ibinyamamukuru vya reta vyamusubiyemwo avuga ko igihugu cugarijwe n’igihe gishasha co kurwanya ico kiza, kandi ko hakenewe inyishu yihariye
 Kuba Ubushinwa  bwahindukiye ku murongo bwahorako mu kurwanya Covid vyatumye prezida Xi arotoherwa, nk’uko abihweza ibintu n’ibindi babibona
 Niwe yari imbere muri poritike ya Covid zero benshi bidogera ko izingamitse ubuzima bwabo bikabije hanyuma igahungabanya ubutunzi
 Ubu naho yayiyehevye, abaraba ibnintu n’ibindi bavuga ategerezwa kwemanga umutwaro w’umupfunda ukomeye w’abandura n’abinjizwa ibitaro
 Benshi baribaza igituma igihugu kititeguye neza gusumba

Dickens Olewe BBC News Igiporisi muri Ghana cagabishije abarongoye ukwemera n’amashengero ko batokora ihishurwa basanzwe bakora ku Mwaka Mushasha kuko hari abo ritera ubwoba, abandi umwitwarariko, mbere abandi bagapfa
 Uburenganzira bwo gusenga ntibutegerezwa kurengera uburenganzira bw’abandi, nk’uko igiporisi cavuze mw’itangazo
 Abanegura iyo ngingo bavuga ko iteye kubiri n’uburenganzira butangwa n’ibwirizwa shingiro mu kwishira no kwizana ku bijanye no kwemera  ko rero iteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Aba-Kristu baharurwa muri za miriyoni akenshi barakoranira mu masengero kugira bumve ivyo  abapasitori  babahishurira ku vyo beretswe ku bizobashikira mu mwaka mushasha
 Hari abahishurirwa ivyiza bibarindiriye ariko hari n’abagabishwa ko barindiriwe n’ivyago
 Iyo ngingo y’igiporisi yatanguye gusohoka mu mwaka uheze igihe abantu bari barengewe n’ukugabishwa kw’impfu n’akaga, nk’uko ikinyamakuru co kuri internet My Joy Online kivyandika
 Mw’itangazo, igiporisi casavye amadini atandukanye”gafashanya” na co no “gukoresha uburyo bwemewe n’amategeko um gushurira ivyo beretswe”
 Ariko umunyamategeko Sammy Sarko yavuze ko  iyo ngingo y’igiporisi “iteye kubiri n’amategeko
” Yanditse ati: “Ntikeneye no kubanza kwihwezwa na sentare ya mbere nkuru muri Ghana
 Nta tegeko muri Ghana riha igiporisi ububasha bwo kugenzura ingene ivyahishuwe bimenyeshwa mu gihugu”
 Yongeyeko ati : “Ubwisanzure bw’idini burenze ubwisanzure bwo gusenga muri sinagoga, isengero canke umusigiti
 Bisigura ko abantu badategerezwa guca kubiri n’ivyo bemera kugira bisunge umuco canke reta kiretse buteye kubiri n’itegeko  iri canke irindi
” Igiporisi cavuze co cashinze itariki ya 27 Kigarama (12) nk’umunsi wo gutangura kwubahiriza ingingo zijanye no kumenyesha ivyahishuwe
 Iryo tangazo ryavuze riti: “Uyu munsi ni uwo kutwibutsa twese, gukora ibikorwa bijanye n’ukwemera hatarenzwe akarimbi k’amategeko kugira hubahirizwe  ituze ridahungabanywa n’umwitwarariko uvuye ku mburi y’ibibi canke urupfu bigiye gushika”

Intambara yo muri Ukraine iri hafi yo kwinjira mu mwaka ugira kabiri
 Ni mu gihe Perezida Vladimir Putin wewe yayiharurira imisi iri ku rushi, ariko ibintu bikaba vyagiye kumuhindukana mu nyuma
 Twabajije abahinga batari bake ba gisirikare ico biyumvira ku kungene ibintu bishobora kugenda ku rubuga mu 2023
 Irashobora kurangira mu mwaka buca utangura,  gute – irashobora kurangirira ku rubuga rw’intambara canke ku meza y’ibiganiro? Canke ishobora no kubandanya gushika mu 2024? Michael Clarke, umwe mu ndongozi z’ikigo Strategic Studies Institute, Exeter, mu Bwongereza Abo bose barondera gutera ikindi gihugu aho ari ho hose mu ceru kinini cane ca Eurasie/Eurasia (ijambo rikoreshwa ku Bulaya na Aziya ubifatiye hamwe nk’umugabane umwe hakuyifata nk’imigabane ibiri), amaherezo baza kwisanga binjiye mu gihe c’ubukonje bakiri mu ntambara
 Napoleon, Hitler na Stalin bose bisanze ibisirikare vyabo bihangana n’ubukonje budasanzwe, kandi n’ubu – mu gihe igitero ciwe kigenda gisubira inyuma ku rubuga - Vladimir Putin ariko ahatira ingabo ziwe kuguma muri ubwo bukonje kugira ngo barindirireho igitero gishasha inyuma y’igihe c’ubukonje
 Impande zompi zirakeneye akaruhuko ariko abanya-Ukraine nibo bafise uburyo buhagije kandi bafise n’ishaka ryo kubandanya urugamba, aha rero tukaba twiteze ko bashobora kubandanya basatira, nibura mu karere ka Donbas
 Mu micungararo ya Kreminna na Svatove bari hafi yo gushika ku ntambwe ikomeye ishobora gutuma ingabo z’Uburusiya zisubira inyuma ku birometero birenga 60, hafi y’ahatanguriye igitero muri Ruhuhuma (2)
 Kyiv ntizokwishimira guhagarika mu gihe ibona intsinzi yegereje
 Hagati aho, ibitero vya Ukraine bishobora guhagarara mu bumanuko bushira uburengero, inyuma yo kwisubiza Kherson
 Kujabuka uruzi Dnipro uja mu buseruko mu ntumbero yo gusatira inzira y’Uburusiya hamwe n’ibarabara ry’indarayi ribufatanya n’akarere ka Crimée/Crimea bishobora gusaba vyinshi
 Ariko ntawofata ko Kyiv idashobora gukora igitero gishasha giturumbuka
 Mu 2023, ikintu nyamukuru kizoba gishingiye ku gitero c’Uburusiya inyuma y’igihe c’ubukonje
 Putin yaremeje ko hafi abasirikare 50
000 bashasha baherutse kwinjizwa mu gisirikare bari bamaze gushika ku rubuga rw’intambara; abandi 250
000 muri abo baherutse kwinjizwa bakaba bari mu nyigisho kugira ngo barungikiwe ku rugamba mu mwaka uza
 Nta kindi gisigaye atari intambara yindi gushika ico izo  ngabo nshasha z’Uburusiya zimaze kigaragariye ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Agahengwe gatoya ariko kadashemeye ni co kindi kintu conyene gishoboka
 Putin aratomora neza ko atazigera ahagarika
 Kandi Ukraine nayo iramenyesha neza ko ikirwanira ukubaho kwayo
 Andrei Piontkovsky, umuhinga akorera i Washington DC Ukraine izotsinda mu kwisubiza ubutavogerwa bwayo bwose bitarenze  inyuma y’igihe c’ubukonje bwa 2023
 Ibintu bibiri bituma twiyumvira gutyo
 Ica mbere ni intego, ishaka n’ubutwari vy’igisirikare ca Ukraine ndetse n’igihugu cose ca Ukraine, bitari bwigere bibaho muri kahise k’intambara ya none
 Ikindi ni uko, inyuma y’imyaka itari mike umutegetsi w’Uburusiya atwaza umukazo, Uburengero bwahavuye bubona uburemere bw’ibibazo bibuhanze muri kazoza
 Ibi birerekanwa neza n’ijambo riheruka gushikirizwa n’umunyamabanga mukuru wa OTAN/NATO, Jens Stoltenberg
 "Igiciro c’ibiriko biraba tukiriha mu mafaranga
 Mu gihe igiciro c’ibiriko biraba abanya-Ukraine bo bakiriha mu maraso
 Mu gihe ibihugu birangwa n’ubutegetsi bw’agahotoro vyobona ko inguvu ari zo zishikana ku co umuntu ashaka,  twese bizodutwara uburyo bwinshi gusumba
 Kandi isi izohinduka ibe isi ibangamye kuri twebwe twese”
 Igihe nyaco c’intsinzi ya Ukraine vyanse bikunze kizovana n’umuvuduko OTAN izofata mu gutanga ibirwanisho nyavyo bishobora guhindura ibintu ku rubuga ( ibimodoka ntamenwa, indege, misire ziraswa kure)
 Niteze ko Melitopol izoba urubuga rw’intambara rukomeye mu mezi ari imbere (canke kumbure amayinga)
 Mu gihe abanya-Ukrane bokwisubiza Melitopol, vyoca biborohera gutera baja ku kiyaga Azov, kugira ngo bace amayira ashikana uburyo n’itumatumanako muri Crimea
 Ivyo kumanika amaboko kw’Uburusiya bizokwumvikanwako mu biganiro vy’abahinga inyuma y’uko abanya-Ukraine bateye intambwe zidasanzwe ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Ibihugu bizoba bitsinze intambara  - Ukraine, Ubwongereza, Amerika – bizoca bishinga iyindi nteguro nshasha y’umutekano mpuzamakungu
 Barbara Zanchetta, igisata kijejwe ivyigwa vy’intambra kw’ishure kaminuza, King's College London Vladimir Putin yari yiteze ko Ukraine itari kuvyura umutwe ngo ihangane n’iki gihugu kibanyi ca rutura, kandi ko ata bindi bihugu vyari kwivanga mu ntambara
 Aha yaharuye nabi, ivyatumye intambara ifata igihe kirekire, aho ivy’uko ishobora kurangira biri kure nk’ukwezi
 Igihe c’ubukonje ntikizokworoha, mu gihe ibitero vy’Uburusiya ku bigo remezo birondera guhagarika ishaka no guca intege abanyagihugu basanzwe barushe
 Ariko uravye ingene abanya-Ukraine bihagarayeko bakivyukiranya ni ibintu bidasanzwe
 Bazokwihagararako
 Intambara izobandanya, yongere ibandanye
 Hari umwijima ku vyerekeye ivy’ibiganiro
 Kugira ngo hashobore kuba amasezerano y’amahoro, ni uko ibintu nyamukuru bisabwa nibura n’uruhande rumwe bihinduka
 Nta kimenyetso na kimwe cerekana ko ibi bishoboka,  canke ko bizohava biba ubu bwa vuba
  None bizohera gute? Uburyo intambara izotwara, haba ku bintu canke ku bantu, birashobora guca intege abanyaporitike b’Uburusiya
 Rero, urupfunguruzo ruri hagati mu Burusiya
 Mu ntambara zo muri kahise zabayemwo uguharura nabi bikagira uruhara rukomeye, nk’intambara yo muri Vietnam kuri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, canke Afghanistan kuri Reta zunze Ubumwe z’Abasoviyeti,  zaje kurangira nk’uku
 Ibintu vyahavuye bihinduka muri poritike y’igihugu cakoze ibiharuro nabi, bituma ciyomora
 Ariko ibi vyoba gusa mu gihe ibihugu vy’uburengero vyohagarara kw’izima bikabandanya bifata mu mugongo Ukraine, mu gihe hagati mu gihugu igitsure kibandanya kubera uburyo iyi ntambara iriko iratwara
 Ikibabaje ni uko izobandanya ari intambara ndende ya poritike, y’ubutunzi n’iya gisirikare aho buri ruhande rutarota rurekura
 Mbere birashoboka ko izoba ikibandanya gushika mu mpera ya 2023
 Ben Hodges, uwahoze arongoye ingabo za Amerika i Bulaya Haracari kare kwiyumvira idefire y’intsinzi i Kyiv ariko ubu Ukraine niyo ifise ibintu mu minwe kandi nta nkeka kuri jewe ko izotsinda iyi ntambara, kumbure mu 2023
 Ibintu bizogenda bukebuke muri kino gihe c’ubukonje, ariko nta nkeka ko ingabo za Ukraine zizovyifatamwo neza gusumba iz’Uburusiya kubera ibikoresho vyose vyo guhangana n’ubukonje bitangwa n’Ubwongereza, Canada n’Ubudagi
 Gushika mu kwa mbere, Ukraine izoba ihagaze neza kugira ngo ishobore gutangura igice ca nyuma c’urugamba, iki naco kikaba ico kubohoza Crimée
 Turazi neza kuva muri kahise ko intambara ari igipimo c’ishaka n’uburyo
 Ndavye ishaka riranga abanyagihugu n’abasirikare ba Ukraine, n’ingene ikibazo c’uburyo kigenda kimera neza ku muvuduko udasanzwe, nta yandi maherezo mbona atari ugutsindwa kw’Uburusiya
 Uburusiya kuvana ingabo muri Kherson vyatumye nshika kuri uno mwanzuro
 Ubwa mbere nk’icongerereza intege abanyagihugu ba Ukraine, ubwa kabiri  nk’ikintu giteje urubwa Kremlin, hanyuma ica gatatu gutuma ingabo za Ukraine zihagarara neza ku rugamba – ubu ibirwanisho Ukraine ifise bikaba biyishoboza kwinjira neza muri Crimée
 Ndizera ko 2023 uzorangira Crimée iri mu minwe ya Ukraine n’aho hashobora kuba amasezerano kanaka ashobora kwemerera Uburusiya kuvana bukebuke ingabo zabwo zirwanira mu mazi muri Sevastopol … mbere igikorwa kigashobora kuzorangirana n’amasezerano (nko mu 2025) yari ahari imbere y’uko Uburusiya bwiyegurira Crimée mu nzira iteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Utwigoro two gusanura tuzoba turiko turabandanya ku nkengera z’ikiyaga ca Azov, harimwo n’ibivuko bikomeye vya Mariupol na Berdyansk, hanyuma gusubira kwugurura umugazo  wa Crimée y’Uburaruko uvana amazi muri Dnipro uyatwara muri Crimée  kikazoba ari ikindi gikorwa nyamukuru kizokwitabwaho
 David Gendelman, umuhinga wa gisirikare ari i Tel Aviv Aho kwibaza “ingene ibintu bizorangira” ng’ibi ivyo buri ruhande rwipfuza gushikako mu gice gikurikira c’intambara
 Ica kabiri conyene c’ingabo 300
000 z’Uburusiya ziherutse kwinjizwa mu gisirikare nizo zimaze kujanwa ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Abandi basigaye, bari kumwe n’abandi bavanywe muri Kherson baha Uburusiya amahirwe yo gutangura ikindi gitero
 Intara za Luhansk na Donetsk zizobandanya ziri mu maboko y’Uburusiya ariko hari amahirwe make ko Uburusiya bushobora gushika ku ntambwe ikomeye nk’iyo kubandanya amaja mu bumanuko gushika mu karere ka Pavlograd kugira ngo bagote ingabo za Ukraine
 Igishoboka cane ni uko amayeri akoreshwa ubu ari yo ashobora kubandanya – kubandanya bacuvya buhoro buhoro ingabo za Ukraine mu duce duto duto hamwe no kubandanya batera intambwe buke buke, nko mu turere twa Bakhmut na Avdiivka, bigashobora kugenda gutyo nyene mu karere ka Svatove-Kreminna
 Kubandanya ibitero ku bigo ntanganguvu vya Ukraine hamwe n’ibindi bitero kuri Ukraine bayiturutse inyuma ni vyo bizorangiza ino ntambara yo gusambura
 Ingabo za Ukraine zitari nke kandi ziridegemvya inyuma y’aho abarusiya baviriye muri Kherson
 Kuri bo, ubu inzira nyamukuru ni iyo gutera baja mu bumanuko, gushika muri Melitopol canke Berdyansk, mu ntumbero yo guca inzira ijana muri Crimée
 Iyo yoba ari intsinzi ikomeye ya Ukraine, kandi ni naco gituma Abarusiya bariko barongereza inguvu muri Melitopol
 Ukraine kandi ishobora guhitamwo kurondera Svatove – mu gihe bokwisubiza ako karere vyoba bibangamiye cane uruhande rwose rw’uburaruko ku rugamba rw’Uburusiya
 Ikibazo gikomeye ni ukumenya ingabo Ukraine ifise ubu kandi zishobora gukora ico gitero ingene zingana muri iki gihe, n’ikirangaminsi Jenerali Zaluzhnyi afise mu nteguro ziwe cerekana ingabo z’integabizoza  ziriko zirategurwa kandi zizoba zimeze magabo mu kwezi kumwe, mu mezi abiri canke atatu uhereye ubu, harimwo abantu, ibiduga vy’intambara n’ibigwanisho biremereye
 Mu gihe urwondo ruzoba rukamutse, niho tuzoronka inyishu kuri iki kibazo
 Kandi iyi nyishu niyo izotwegereza buke buke ku “kungene bizorangira”
