Na Raffi Berg BBC News Ubushinwa  bwavogereye ku rugero rutari bwigere rubaho amazi n’ibirere  vya Taiwan, nk’uko reta yayo ibivuga
 Ivuga ko indege 71 z’igisirikare kirwanira mu kirere, harimwo iz’intambara na zimwe zitagira abadereva (drones), zinjiye mu citwa akarere ka Taiwan ko gucungereramwo ikirere
 Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zivuga ko iki gikorwa ca gisirikare c’Ubushinwa ari ico “guhungabanya” kandi gitosekaza “amahoro n’umutekano mu karere”
 Taiwan irigenga – ariko Ubushinwa buyifata nk’intara ishaka kwiyonkora, kandi ko impera n’imperuka izosubizwa mu ruhongore
 Muri ano mezi ya vuba, icuka kibi cariyongereye hagati y’izi mpande zibiri
 Muri Myandagaro (8), Pékin/Beijing (umugwa mukuru w’Ubushinwa) yararakajwe n’urugendo umukuru w’inama nshingamateka ya Amerika Nancy Pelosi yakoze muri iryo zinga, umutegetsi wa mbere mukuru wa Amerika yari agendeye Taiwan mu myaka 25
 Mu kwihora kuri urwo rugendo, Ubushinwa bwakoze imyimenyerezo ya gisirikare ya mbere ikomeye mu mazi akikuje Taiwan, yongera ihagarika n’ubudandaji bumwe bumwe n’iryo zinga
 Umushikiranganji wa Taiwan ajejwe imigenderanire Joseph Wu yariyamirije ico gikorwa c’Ubushinwa ico gihe, aho yavuze ko ari agasotoro ko ku rwego rwo hejuru
 Ubushinwa ntiburigera buvuga ko butazohava bukoresha inguvu kugira ngo bwigarurire Taiwan
 Ejo ku wa mbere, umushikiranganji wa Taiwan ajejwe kvivuna abansi yavuze ko indege 43 zajabutse umurongo wo hagati, akarere kigenga kagabura impande zibiri
 Ubushinwa buvuga ko bwakoze “imyimenyerezo yo kurasa” mu micungararo ya Taiwan ku wa Mungu mu kwihora ico buvuga ko kari agasomborotso k’iryo zinga na Amerika
 Umutegetsi wa Maison Blanche/White House ari mu Nama nkuru y’igihugu ijejwe umutekano avuga ko Amerika irajwe ishinga n’ibi bintu biherutse kuba, akongerako y’uko “izobandanya ifasha Taiwan mu gukomeza ubushobozi bwayo bwo kwirwanako”
 Washington yamye na ntaryo yinengesera kuri kino kibazo ca Taiwan
 Ku ruhande rumwe, irashigikira poritike y’igihugu kimwe c’Ubushinwa, inkingi y’ubucuti na Pékin
 Muri ino poritike, Amerika iremera ko hari reta imwe y’Ubushinwa, kandi ikaba ifitaniye ubucuti buzwi na Pékin hakubugiriranira na Taiwan
 Hagati aho, ibandanya ifitaniye ubucuti bwa hafi cane na Taiwan, mbere ikanayigurishako ibirwanisho mu masezerano yiswe Taiwan Relations Act ( mu Kirundi twogereranya na ‘Itegeko rigenga imigenderanire na Taiwan’), akaba avuga ko Amerika itegerezwa guha iryo zinga uburyo bwo kwivuna umwansi

