Igihuhusi gikomeye c'urubura cugarije Amerika ya Ruguru catumye igisagara ca Buffalo, mu ntara ya New York, gisa n'ahariko harabera intambara, nk'uko bivugwa n'umukuru w'iyo ntara
 Ku wa mbere, ico gisagara caharuye abantu 25 bahitanywe n'impfu ziturutse kuri ico kirere kibi, mu gihe ku wa Mungu bari 13 gusa
 Ico gihusi kiva muri Canagigashika mu bumanuko nk'i Rio Grande kimaze guhitana abantu 50 mu gihugu cose
 Abakurikirana ingene ikirere gihinduka bavuga ko ico gihuhusi kizoturura mu minsi mike iri imere ariko abantu n’ubu bagirirwa inama yo kwirinda gufata ingendo kiretse ari nkenerwa cane
 Ico gihuhusi cari kimaze iminsi cahungabanije ibintu ariko ubu umuyagankuba uriko uragaruka inyuma y’iminsi abantu bari mu kizime
 Abakiriya hafi 200
000 ntibagira umuyagankuba kuva ku wa Mungu inyuma ya sasita (mu masaha yo mu buseruko bwa  Amerika na Canada) bavuye kuri miriyoni 1
7, nk’uko vyandikwa n’itororokanirizo Associated Press
 Ingendo ibihumbi z’indege zarahagaritswe, bituma abantu benshi badashobora gushikira imiryango yabo ngo basangira Noeli
 Abanyamerika miriyoni 55 ku wa mungu bari bagifise imburi z’uko hari igihuhusi c’imbeho
 Umukuru w’intara ya New York Kathy Hochul asanzwe avuka Buffalo – yavuze ati: “Bigiye mu mateka nk’igihuhusi ca mbere gikomeye muri kahise ka Buffao
” Yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ku wa Mungu ku mugoroba ati: “Uhashitse umenga ni ahabereye intambara, imiduga kw’ibarabara nayo iteye agahinda
” Yavuze ko abahaba n’ubu boguma mu mazu kuko uko ibintu bikimeze “umuntu ashobora kuhasiga ubuzima”
 Umuryango umwe ufise abana bakiri bato -b'imyaka iri hagati ya  2 na 6 - barindiriye amasaha 11 imbere y'uko batabarwa mu masaha ya kare yo ku munsi wa Noel
 Se w'abana,  Zila Santiago, yabwiye CBS News ati: "Mu vy'ukuri nari nataye icizere''
 Yavuze ko bagumye basusurutse kuko yaretse imoteri ikaguma yaka hanyuma akagwanya kwihebura mu gukina n'abana
 Vyitezwe ko abandi benshi bahuye n'akaga c'ico gihuhusi bazotorwa niyo ibirundo vy'urubura vyamara gushonga gutyo bikagaragaza abagotewe mu miduga no mu ngo ziri kure
 Impfu ziturutse kuri ico gihuhusi c’urubura zaravuzwe kandi muri Vermont, Ohio, Missouri, Winsconsin, Kansas na Colardo
 Ubushushe muri Florida y’ubumanuko bwarakorotse cane gushika aho  imiserabanyi izwi nka iguana icika ibuye igakoroka iva ku biti
 Intara ya Montana mu burengero bwa Amerika niyo ibabajwe cane n’iyo mbeho kurusha ahandi , aho ubushuhe bwagabanutse gushika kuri degre 45 munsi y’ubusa (-45C)
 Muri Canada, intara za Ontario na Quebec nizo zibabaye cane
 Muri Quebec abakiriya bashika 120
000 nta muyagankuba bari bafise ku wa Mungu
 Abategetsi bavuga ko bishobora gufata iminsi imbere y’uko ingo zimwe zimwe zisubizwa ku mirongo y’umuyagankuba

Igitero ca Ukraine ikoresheje indege itagira umudereva (drone) kw'ikambi y’indege z’intambara ya Engels mu bumanuko bw’Uburusiya cahitanye abantu batatu, nk’uko bivugwa na Moscou
 Igisata gicungera ikirere c’Uburusiya kivuga ko cakoroye iyo drone ariko ko ibisigarira vyayo vyakorotse bikiha inkumbi muri ico gitero cabaye mw’ijoro ryakeye
 Mu ntango za kuno kwezi, Uburusiya bwaragirije Ukraine igitero nk’ico kuri iyo kambi ibitse indege zitera amabombe
 Iyo kambi iri ku birometero 500 uvuye ku rubibe rwa Ukraine mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko
 Igisirikare ca Ukraine ntaco kiravuga ku mugaragaro kuri ibi bitero
 Ubushikiranganji bw’Uburusiya bujejwe kwivuna abansi  buvuga ko igisirikare cabwo kirwanira mu kirere cakoroye iyi drone ya Ukraine yagendera hafi hafi isaha indwi n’iminota 35 z’ijoro (01:35) mu masaha yo muri ico gihugu kuri uno wa mbere, nk’uko bubivuga
 Abasirikare batatu b’Uburusiya nibo bapfuye biturutse ku bikomere vyatewe n’ibisigarira vy’iyi drone, nk’uko ubu bushikiranganji bubivuga
 Buramatari w’intara ya Saratov Roman Busargin arahoza imiryango n’incuti z’aba basirikare, akavuga ko ata “mutekano ugeramiwe” ku basanzwe baba mu gisagara ca Engels
 Imbere y’aha, abakoresha imbuga hwaniro basohoye amavidewo yerekana ivyumvikana nk’ibisasu n’amafirimbi yo kugabisha (sirènes) ku kibuga c’indege ca Engels
 Mu kindi gitero cavuzwe ku wa 05 Kigarama (12) kuri ico kibuga c’indege, be no ku yindi kambi y’indege z’intambara mu ntara ya Ryazan, abasirikare batatu barishwe naho nyene n’ibisigarira vya drone ya Ukraine yakorowe, nk’uko vyavuzwe na Moscou ico gihe
 Indege zibiri nizo zononekaye bukebuke
 Igisirikare ca Ukraine ntaco cavuze kuri ivyo bitero
 Ikambi ya Engels isanzwe ikoreshwa n’Uburusiya mu gutera ibisasu vya misire ku bibanza bitari bike vya Ukraine kuva Moscou itanguye intambara yayo ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2)
 Kremlin iramaze kwagiriza Ukraine gutera ubutaka bwayo, ariko ibi bitero vyo muri Kigarama vyabaye imbere cane mu Burusiya gusumba ivy’imbere y’aha
 Abahinga batari bake ba gisirikare muri Ukraine no mu Burengero babona ko ibi bitero bivugwa ari inkuru mbi ku gisirikare c’Uburusiya

Amashirahamwe atanu makuru makuru yahagaritse ibikorwa muri Afghanistan inyuma y’aho aba Taliban baburije abakozi b’abagore muri yo
 Amashirahamwe Care International, Norwegian Refugee Council (NRC) hamwe na Save the Children avuga ko adashobora kubandanya ibikorwa vyayo “abakozi bacu b’abagore batarimwo”
 International Rescue Committee (IRC) naryo nyene ryahagaritse ibikorwa, mu gihe irindi naryo Islamic Relief rivuga ko ryahagaritse hafi ibikorwa vyaryo vyose
 Ubutegetsi bw’aba Taliban muri Afghanistan burageramiye uburenganzira bw’abagore
 Iri tegeko ku mashirahamwe y’abagiraneza rije inyuma y’imisi mikeya aba Taliban babujije abagore kwiga amashure kaminuza
 Abdel Rahman Habib, umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bw’ubutunzi muri reta y’aba Taliban, yagiriza abagore bakora mu mashirahamwe mpuzamakungu y’abagiraneza ko bahonyanga amabwirizwa mu kutambara hijab, wa mwambaro wo kwitwikira w’aba-Islam
 Aba Taliban bagabisha ko bashobora guhagarika impusha kw’ishirahamwe iryo ari ryo ryose ritokurikiza ubwo nyene iyi ngingo
 Amashirahamwe atari make ariyamiriza iyi ngingo, agasaba ko abagore bokwemererwa kubandanya bakorana nayo
 Abarongoye Care, NRC na Save the Children bavuze mw’itangazo rusangi ko aya mashirahamwe atari “kuba yashikiriye amamiriyoni n’amamiriyoni y’abanya-Afghanistani bakeneye ubufasha kuva muri Myandagaro (8) 2021” iyo hataba abakozi b’abagore
 Iri tangazo ryabo rivuga kandi riti: "Mu gihe tumaze kuronka umuco kuri iri tangazo, turahagaritse vy’agateganyo ibikorwa vyacu, dusaba ko abagabo n’abagore bose ku buringanire bobandanya ibikorwa vy’ubutabazi muri Afghanistan”
 Ku ruhande rwayo, IRC isanzwe ikoresha abagore 3000 mu gihugu cose ivuga ko ubushobozi bwayo mu bikorwa vyayo bwari buhagaze ku “bakozi b’abagore ku ngero nzose mw’ishirahamwe ryacu”, ko rero mu gihe abagore batokwemererwa gukora, idashobora gushikira “abo bose bakeneye ubufasha”
 Islamic Relief rivuga ko ryafashe “ingingo itoroshe yo guhagarika vy’agateganyo ibikorwa vyose atari ivyo ubutabazi muri Afghanistan” harimwo  “ibikorwa vyo gufasha imiryango ya ba ntahonikora kuronka amaragamo, co kimwe n’ibijanye n’indero n’ibindi bimwe bimwe vy’amagara y’abantu”
 Iri shirahamwe rivuga riti: "Islamic Relief isaba abategetsi ba Afghanistan guhagarika vuba bwango iyi ngingo yo kubuza abakozi b’abagore mu mashirahamwe y’abagiraneza”
 "Iyi ngingo izogira ingaruka mbi cane ku mamiriyoni y’abagabo, abagore n’abana mu gihugu cose
 Turababaye kubona iyi ngingo ije inyuma y’imisi mike gusa hafashwe izindi ngingo ruhasha zo kuzibira abakobwa mu mashure”
 Ramiz Alakbarov, umugenduzi mukuru w’igisata kijejwe ubutabazi mw’ishirahamwe ONU avuga ko ONU iriko iragerageza gusaba ko iyi ngingo ifutwa kandi ko ari “umurongo utukura ku mashirahamwe yose y’abagiraneza”
 ONU irashobora guhagarika ibikorwa vyo gutanga imfashanyo mur Afghanistan mu gihe aba Taliban batofuta iyi ngingo ibuza abagore gukora mu mashirahamwe y’abagiraneza, nk’uko uyo mutegetsi yabibwiye BBC
 Ariko Alakbarov avuga ko bitaratomoka neza ico aba Taliban bashatse kuvuga muri iyo ngingo
 Avuga ko umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu muri reta y’aba Taliban yabwiye ishirahamwe ONU ko ryobandanya ibikorwa vyaryo bijanye n’amagara y’abantu kandi ko abagore bashobora “kubandanya batonda ku kazi bagakora ibikorwa vyabo”
 Yongerako y’uko n’ubundi bushikiranganji na bwo nyene bwivuganiye na ONU, aho buvuga ko ibikorwa mu bisata vyo guhangana n’ibiza be n’ivy’ubutabazi  vyobandanya ukuri kwamye
 Jan Egeland wo muri NRC avuga ko hafi 500 b’abakozi 1400 b’iri shirahamwe ry’abagiraneza ari abagore, kandi ko abakozi b’abagore bakora “bakurikije imico n’imigenzo yose, amabwirizwa ajanye n’inyambaro, ukwiyunguruza, no gutandukanya ibiro bakoreramwo”
 Avuga ko yizeye ko iyi ngingo ishobora “gufutwa mu misi iri imbere”, anagabisha ko amamiriyoni n’amamiriyoni y’abanyagihugu bomererwa nabi mu gihe amashirahamwe y’abagiraneza yozibirwa
 Kuva bisubije ubutegetsi bw’igihugu mu mwaka uheze, aba Taliban babandanya bazingamika uburenganzira bw’abagore – n’aho bari bemereye amakungu ko ubutegetsi bwabo buzokwiyorosha gusumba ubutegetsi bwabo bwo mu myaka ya 1990
 Uretse abagore kubuzwa mu mashirahamwe y’abagiraneza no mu mashure ya kaminuza – mbere nko ku banyeshure hoho, abajejwe umutegako bakaba ari bo bahagarariye iyi ngingo – amashure yisumbuye y’abakobwa aracugaye mu ntara hafi zose z’igihugu
 Abagore kandi ntibemerewe kwinjira ibibanza vyo gufatiramwo akayaga n'amazu yo kwinonoreramwo imitsi, ivyo ni bimwe mu bibanza bihuriramwo abantu benshi batarekuriwe kujamwo

Inyuma y’imisi ijana itanguye, imyiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza ubutegetsi imaze igihe kirekire kuva habaye impinduka za ki-Islam muri Irani mu 1979 irahungabanije ubutegetsi ariko ku kiguzi kinini c’ubuzima bw’abantu imaze guhitana
 Abarenga 500 bari muri yo, harimwo abana 69 baramaze kwicwa, nk’uko bivugwa n’ishirahamwe riharanira agateka ka zina muntu, Human Rights Activists' News Agency, HRANA
 Babiri muri yo baramaze kunyongwa abandi nabo bababa 26 barindiriye igihano nk’ico, mu co ishirahamwe Amnesty International rivuga ko ari "imanza z’amanyanga"
 N’aho hari imyiyerekano yari imaze kuba muri kahise igahungabanya Irani – mu 2017 gushika mu ntango za 2018, hamwe n’iyindi yo muri Munyunyo (11) 2019 – iya kino gihe ntisanzwe, kuko ihuriyemwo abanyagihugu bo mu gihugu cose kandi abagore bakaba ari bo bafashe iya mbere ku civugo kivuga ngo “Abagore, Ubuzima, Ubwigenge”
 Impande zompi zafashe umurongo utoroshe, ubutegetsi butuza abari muri yo, aho abadahunze bapfungwa, bakaborezwa igufa, abapfa bagapfa
 Bamwe mu bihangange vya Irani bafashe ingingo zo gushigikira imyiyerekano, ivyatumye bafatwa canke bakomoka
 Taraneh Alidoosti, umukinyi w’amareresi azwi cane, apfungiwe mw’ibohero rizwi cane rya Evin  inyuma yo kwiyamiriza inyongwa ry’umuyabaga yari mu myiyerekano
 Imbere y’aha, uyu mugore yari yasohoye isanamu yiwe atambaye igitambara co kwitwikira mu mutwe nk’uko bitegerezwa, afise n’igicapo kiriko icivugo c’iyi myiyerekano
 Asghar Farhadi yahagarariye Alidoosti mw’ireresi yiwe, The Salesman, yanditse ku rubuga rwa Instagram ati: "Narakoranye na Taraneh mu mareresi ane none ubu ari mw’ibohero kubera ashigikiye bagenziwe mu gihugu, be no kwiyamiriza imanza z’akarenganyo ziriko ziracibwa”
 "Nimba kwerekana ko ushigikiye uwuharanira uburenganzira bwiwe ari icaha, ubwo rero amamiriyoni mirongo y’abanyagihugu muri kino gihugu ni abagizi ba nabi”
 Uwundi mukinyi w’amareresi  azwi cane yahunze igihugu, Pegah Ahangarani yabwiye BBC ati: "Irani ntishobora gusubira mu gihe c’imbere ya Mahsa Amini", akaba ashaka kuvuga igihe c’umugore w’umunya-Iran iw’umu-kurde yapfiriye mw’ibohero ku wa 19 Nyakanga (9) bigaca bitera imyiyerekano
 Hamid Farrokhnezhad, uwundi mukinyi w’amareresi w’umunya-Irani azwi cane, yahungiye muri Amerika muri kuno kwezi, avuga ko Indongozi y’ikirenga wa Irani, Ali Khamenei, ari "umutegetsi w’agahotoro"
 Amugereranya na Franco yahoze arongoye Espagne, Stalin yahoze arongoye Uburusiya, be na Mussolini yahoze arongoye Ubutaliyano, abo bose bakaba bazwi nk’abari barongoye intwaro mbi z’agahotoro
 Ikindi kintu gitandukanya iyi myiyerekano n’iyabaye imbere y’aha, ni uko abri muri yo batanguye gukoresha vya biturika bihingurwa mu bitoro (cocktail Molotov)
 Ibi biherutse gukoreshwa ku birindiro vy’umurwi witwara gisirikare  Basija hamwe na Hawza, canke amashure y’idini yegukira abarongoye ishami rya Islam  ry’aba Shia
 Umurwi uzwi nka Generation Z nawo warafashe iya mbere muri ino myiyerekano, mu kurenga ku mabwirizwa ruhasha y’idini itanguza ibindi bikorwa bisadanzwe nko guturira ibitambara vyo mu mutwe vyambarwa n’abategetsi b’aba-Islam
 Uwundi murwi ugizwe n’urwaruka ni uwitwa "turban tossing" (twogereranya mu Kirundi na gukorora ibitambara) – aho abari muri wo bayomboka bagaca inyuma y’abategetsi b’Abashia, bagakubita ku bitambara vyabo bagaca biruka
 Umusore w’imyaka 16, Arshia Emamgholizadeh, yarahagaritswe mu gisagara ca Tabriz  kiri mu buraruko bushira uburengero mu kwezi guheze yagirizwa “gukorora igitambara”
 Yapfunzwe imisi cumi imbere yo gupfungurwa
 Haciye imisi ibiri, yariyahuye, ivyo umuryago wiwe uvuga ko vyatewe n’ingene yafashwe nabi mw’ibohero
 Igihe yari apfunzwe, Arshia yarakubiswe amahiri yongera ahabwa n’ibinini bitazwi, nk’uko umwe mu begereye umuryango yabibwiye BBC igisata c’ururimi rw’igi perse
 Mehran Samak w’imyaka 27 yararashwe mu mutwe mu gisagara ca Bandar Anzali kiri mu buraruko kubera yavugije ihona mu kwerekana umunezero igihe Irani itsindwa ikava mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose, mu rukino rwabaye ku wa 29 Munyonyo
 Gushika ubu, abagabo babiri ni bo bamaze kunyongwa inyuma yo kwagirwa n’ivyaha vyo guhungabanya umutekano bifatiye kuri ino myiyerekano,  mu co abaharanira agateka ka zina muntu bavuga ko ari amakosa akomeye y’ubucamanza
 Abenshi mu bamaze gucirwa manza zo gupfa bavuga ko bakorewe iyica rubozo

Na George Wright BBC News Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zagiriza Korea ya Ruguru ko yahaye umuhari Wagner w’abacangero b’Abarusiya ibisasu vya misire na vya muzinga ukoresha mu ntambara muri Ukraine
 Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu ca Amerika) ivuga ko irungikwa ry’ivyo birwanisho rihonyanga ivyemezo vy’Inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano kw’isi, kandi ko igiye gutangaza ibindi bihano kuri Wagner
 Yaba Korea ya Ruguru, yaba umuhari Wagner, bompi barahakana aya makuru
 Abarwanyi b’uyu muhari bariyongereye kuva ku 1000 gushika hafi ku 20
000 muri Ukraine, nk’uko bivugwa na Reta y’Ubwongereza
 Uyu murwi kandi urakorera muri Syria no mu bihugu vya Afrika, ukama wagirizwa ivyaha vyo mu ntambara n’ihohotera rya kiremwa muntu
 Umuvugizi wa Maison Blanche, John Kirby , yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Wagner iriko irarondera abayiha ibirwanisho kw’isi yose mu bikorwa vyayo vya gisirikare muri Ukraine"
 Ati: "Turashobora kwemeza ko Korea ya Ruguru yamaze guheza kurungikira Wagner ibirwanisho vya mbere, ikaba yaramaze no kubiriha”
 Maison Blanche ivuga ko uyu murwi w’abacangero wakiriye ibisasu vya muzinga na misire wahawe na Korea ya Ruguru
 Kirby  avuga ko Wagner ikoresha imiriyoni zirenga 100 z’amadorari y’Abanyamerika buri kwezi muri Ukraine
 Avuga kandi ko uyu murwi ubangabanganywe n’igisirikare c’Uburusiya mu bukomezi
 Umushikiranganji w’Ubwongereza ajejwe imigenderanire y’iki gihugu James Cleverly avuga ko Londres yemera uwu mwihwezo wa Washington
 Mw’itangazo, Cleverly  avuga ati: "Kubona Perezida [Vladimir] Putin yikora kuri Korea ya Ruguru ngo imufashe, ni ikimenyetso ko Uburusiya butorohewe kandi ko isi yabwagiye”
 Ariko, nyen’umuhari Wagner, Yevgeny Prigozhin, arahakana aya makuru, akavuga ko ari “igihuha”, nayo ubushikiranganji bwa Korea ya Ruguru bujejwe imigenderaire buvuga ko aya makuru ata “shingiro” afise
 Umuvugizi wa Korea ya Ruguru avuga ko iki gihugu kitarahindura aho gihagaze kandi ko ihererekanwa ry’ibirwanisho hagati ya Korea ya Ruguru n’Uburusiya “ritarigera ribaho”
 Umuhari Wagner uzwi ko watanguye kuja mu bikorwa igihe Uburusiya bwigarurira Crimée/Crimea mu  2014
 Nyenewo, Prigozhin, ni umutunzi ruhebwa azwi nk’”umwishikira kwa Putin”
 Uruhara rwa Wagner rwagiye rukomera cane mu gihe Uburusiya bugenda butakaza mu ntambara yabwo muri Ukraine
 Muri Ntwarante (3), 2022, Wagner yavugwa ko yari yarungitse abarwanyi barenga gato 1000
 Ariko abategetsi b’Ubwongereza bavuga ko iki gitigiri ciyongereye gushika kuri 20
000, hafi ic’icumi (1/10) c’ingabo z’Uburusiya ziri ku rugamba
 Igituma ibitigiri vya Wagner bigenda vyiyongera ni ukubera igenda irondera abarwanyi mu mpfungwa ziri mu mabohero y’Uburusiya
 Benshi mu bakubiswe intahe mu gahanga bavugwa ko baciye binjira muri Wagner – n’aho ata biharuro nyezina bizwi
 Babwirwa ko bazohembwa kandi ko bazohanagurwako ibihano baciriwe  inyuma y’amezi atandatu bari ku rugamba

Igikorwa co gusezera no gushingura umunyamuziki rutura wo muri Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo cabandanije n'aho sentare yari yabanje gufata ingingo yo kugisivya ku busabe bw’umuryango
 Umwe mu bavugizi b’umuryango yabwiye ibinyamakuru ko babandanije bavugana n’umushikirizamanza kugira ngo atange uruhusha ko ibikorwa vyo gushingura Tshala Muana bibandanya kuri uno wa gatanu
 Umuryango wiwe w’amaraso, wari washatse guhagarika ishingurwa ryiwe, usa n’uwemeye ko integuro zibandanya uko zitegekanijwe kuri uno wa gatanu bifashijwemwo n'umutambukanyi wa Joseph Kabila
 Urwandiko rwari rwasohowe na sentare kuri uno wa gatanu, rwategeka ibitaro kudatanga ikiziga
 Ni  inyuma y’aho umuryango w’amaraso witwariye umukunzi wa Tshala Muana, Claude Mashala, ari na we yamufasha gusohora indirimbo, umwagiriza ko yihereranije igikorwa co kumushingura, atavyumvikanyeko n’umuryango w’amaraso
 Ibintu vyagiye guhinduka ku munota wa nyuma aho umutambukanyi wa Joseph Kabila yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu, Olive Lembe -azwi ko ari incuti ya hafi cane y’umuryango wa Tshala Muana -  avyinjiriyemwo agashobora kwumvisha uwo muryango ko wogenza buhoro
 Inyuma y’imyaka itari mike abica bigacika mu muziki, Élisabeth Tshala Muana Muidikay, yari asanzwe azwi kw’izina rya Tshala Muana, yapfuye ku wa 10 z’uku kwezi nyene afise imyaka 64 y’amavuko
