 Kibumba iri ku birometero 25 mu buraruko bwa Goma, kikaba ari co kirindiro cari cegereye igisagara ca Goma
 Yari yafashwe inyuma y’intambara zabaye hagati mu kwezi kwa Munyonyo (11)
 M23 yatumyeko abanyamakuru mu masaha ari imbere kuri uno wa gatanu kugira ngo birabire ingene ishikiriza iki gisagara
 Mw’iryo tangazo, umuhari M23 ukengurukira abategetsi b’akarere ku twigoro twabo two kurondera inyishu iciye mu mahoro ku ndyane ziri mu buseruko bw’ico gihugu
 Umenyesha ko ufashe iyo ngingo “y’ubugwaneza” mu ntumbero yo gukurikiza ivyasabwe n’inama y’abakuru b’ibihugu vy'akarere yabaye ku wa 23 Munyonyo uno mwaka ku mugwa mukuru wa Angola, Luanda
 Abakuru b’ibihugu vy’akarere bategetse umuhari M23 guhagarika intambara no kuva mu turere wari wigaruriye, nk’imwe mu ngingo zikomeye zafashwe muri iyo nama yabo
 Mu gihe Urwanda rubandanya rwagirizwa gufasha uyu muhari mu kuwuha ibirwanisho n’abantu narwo rukabandanya ruvyiyamiriza rwivuye inyuma, abo bakuru b’ibihugu barerekanye impungenge ku kungene M23 ibandanya ironka ibirwanisho bihanitse n’ubundi buryo buyituma ikora ibitero ku ngabo za Congo
 Aba bakuru b’ibihugu vy’akarere bari bakoraniye muri iyo nama ya Luanda muri Angola, bemeje ko mu gihe M23 itokurikiza ivyo bayitegeka bazoca basaba ingabo z’akarere ko zikoresha inguvu
