Hari itariki 8 Nyakanga (ukwezi kw'icenda) mu 2018, ku wa gatanu
 Umumenyeshamakuru Marciane Pereira Dos Santos w'imyaka 36, ico gihe, yashitse arushe avuye ku kazi, ari kumwe n'abana biwe babiri b'imyaka ibiri n'itanu
 Imbere yo kwinjira mu nzu yabamwo, muri kartiye ya Jardin Tropical, i Serra, yegerewe n'umugabo bahorana, bari bamaze amezi atatu bahukanye inyuma y'imyaka indwi bubakanye, biturutse mu guturubikwa
 Kubera ukubabazwa n'ukuba baravanye, ariko bakabandanya baba kw'ibarabara rimwe, uwo mugabo yashatse ko Marciane amuha insiguro aho amenyeye ko yatanguye kugendana n'uwundi mugaabo
 Kugira yirinde gutangura gushwana n'uwahora ari umugabo wiwe abana babona, uwo mumenyeshamakuru yaciye aja kubabitsa ku mubanyi
 "Ntashe iwanje, nasanze andindiriye imbere y'inzu duca dutangura gushwana
 Yaciye anyegera afise imbugita, aca ansukako umuti aca arandomeka
 Sinaronse n'umwanya wo kugira ico nkoze, ico nibuka gusa ni uko nabonye urubeya rurabije umubiri wanje uca utangura kwaka", nk'uko avyibuka
 Marciane Pereira yibuka ko yaciye agwa hasi atangura kwikumbagaza mw'ibarabara rya kaburimbo kugira arabe ko imbeya zozima
 Haheze akanya bumva amaborogo, ababanyi baragerageje kumufasha mu gusuka mu kumusukako amazi
 Uwo mugore yarahiye ku rugero rwa kabiri n'urwa gatatu mu maso, kw'izosi, umutumba, amaguru n'amaboko
 Umubiri wiwe warahiye gushika hafi ku 40%
 Ati: "Muri ico gihe cose nagumanye ubwenge, kandi nta kindi niyumvira atari abana banje"
 Kubera ubushe bukabije, Marciane yamaze muri koma (coma) amezi atatu, mw'ivuriro ry'abaremvye cane aho yari hagati y'ubuzima n'urupfu
 Amaze kwikangura, yongeye amara ayandi mezi abiri naho nyene aremvye
 Uwo mumyenyeshamakuru yabazwe incuro 18 hanyuma aracibwa ukuguru kw'i bubamfu kubera ubushe bukabije, ubu akaba asigaye yiyunguruza n'ikinga ry'abagendana ubumuga (fauteuil roulant/wheel chair)
 Asigura ati: "N'ubu ndacarindiriye  kubagwa kugira basanasane neza izuru, umunwa n'amatwi vyanje
 "Aho sinvuze ivyo ntegerezwa gukorerwa ku maboko n'ibiganza kugira nongereze ukwikomakoma kuko gushika ubu ndabishobora buke buke cane
 Nari kuba namaze kubagwa ukuboko, ariko umunsi vyategerezwa kuba, naciye ngwara Covid-19, gushika ubu nkaba ntarasubira gushobora kubishira kuri gahunda"
 "N'ubwo umubiri wanje wahindutse, sinigeze ngira ingorane zo kwiraba mu cirori
 Ingorane nyamukuru mfise, ni ubumuga bw'umubiri bwatewe n'ico caha, na cane cane ingorane zo kwitaho abana banje", nk'uko abandanya avuga
 Marciane  ni nyina w'umuhungu w'imyaka itandatu, umuhungu w'umugabo yamuturiye, n'umukobwa w'imyaka icenda
 Ico caha kimaze kuba, uwo yahoze ari umugabo wa Marciane yarasfashwe n'igiporisi hanyuma avuga ko ivyashitse vyatewe n'ishari
 Mu kwezi kw'umunani uwo mugabo yaraciriwe urubanza ahanishwa  gupfungwa imyaka 32
 Urubanza rwamaze amasaha arenga umunani mu ntahe yari igizwe n'abantu indwi, abagabo bane n'abagore batatu
 Marciane niho yari ari kugira arabane imbona nkubone n'uwahoze ari umugabo wiwe ubwa mbere kuva ico caha kibaye
 "Igihe namubona naramubajije niba yibuka ingene twari twavanye hanyuma avuga ko atavyo azi
 Cari igihe kibabaje cane
 Kandi naho nari nzi ko bitazokworoha na gato, nibaza ko tutari twigeze twitegurira bene ivyo bihe", nk'uko uwo mumenyeshamakuru avyibuka
 Ku bw'uwo mugore, bagitangura kubana, uwo mugabo yari umuntu w'igikundiro kandi yari umuntu atuje
 N'ubwo atari yarigeze ahutazwa ku mubiri imbere y'ico caha, Marciane avuga ko uko umwanya wahaca, umugabo yatanguye  inyifato yo kurondera kumwihariza no kumuturubika
 "Yaramvuma, agatorogana ariko nkamwemera kuko namukunda (


) Vyari ibihe vy'ishavu, sinabifata nko nkunturubika
 Abantu bavuga ko atari vyiza
 Ariko vy'ukuri sinabona ibiriko biraba mu buzima bwanje
 Nico gituma bikenewe kwumviriza abantu barabira ubuzima bwanyu hanze, kuko barabona ibiriko biraba hatagiyemwo kubirabisha amaso y'urukundo", nk'uko avuga
 Mu gihe atagishoboye gukora, Marciane akoresha umwanya wiwe wose mu kwitaho abana biwe no gufasha abandi bagore bahura n'amabi yo mu ngo canke babayeho bafatwa ukutari ko
 Marciane asigura ati: "Ndemesha amanama ku mabi yo mu ngo, nkavugana n'abagore bahanzwe n'ibisana n'ivyo naciyemwo hanyuma ngakoresha imbuga hwaniro kugira nkangurire abantu izo ngorane hanyuma ntange ubutumwa bwo kuremesha ababanye bafatwa ukutari ko
 Nkoresha ivyanshikiye mu kubumvisha ko bomenya ingaruka ziva ku kubana gutyo
 Marciane yamye yifuza kwiga amashure, ariko kubera ingorane z'uburyo bw'amafaranga, ntiyigeze yiga amashure ya kaminuza
 Ivyo vyarahindutse uyu mwaka, kuva aho aronkeye  abamurihira amashure kw'ishure rya kaminuza mu gisagara ubu akaba yaratanguye kwiga ibikorwa vy'imibano
 Avuga ati: "Haraheze imyaka mirongo ibiri, ubwo nariko ndakora nk'umukozi wo mu rugo, umunsi umwe umugabo yankoresha yambariye ngo nta kindi ndi atari umukozi wo mu rugo, ko rero ntota umwanya mu kwiga
 Ameherezo navyemeye indoto zanje nca ndaheba
 Ariko ubu, nibaza ko nshobora kwiga hanyuma ngashobora kuba ico nifuza" 
 "Ubutumwa bwanje ngaha ni ukwiga hanyuma, nk'umukozi w'ivyerekeye imibano, ndashobora gufasha mu buzima bw'abantu"
 Umunsi mpuzamakungu wahariwe kurwanya amabi akorerwa abagore uhimbazwa itariki 25 Munyonyo (11) kuva mu 1999
 Washinzwe n'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU kugira uhimirize abantu kwitaho ico kibazo
 Ariko n'ubwo hari utwigoro two guhimiriza abagore n'abagabo kuri ico kibazo, ibiharuro vy'amabi akorerwa abagore  biracateye agahinda
 Ni ukwihenda kwibaza ko amabi akorerwa umugore ari ayo ku mubiri gusa, ashobora kuba ayo guturubika, ayafatiye ku gitsina, ku kuremerwa [n'ivyo bakuvugako canke bakubwira] canke ku butunzi

Ukraine ni "nzima kandi ihagaze neza” kandi ntizigera imanika amaboko, niko Perezida Volodymyr yavuze, mw’ijambo yashikirije imbere y’inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka za Amerika mu rugendo rwiwe rwa mbere rwo hanze y’igihugu kuva Uburusiya butanguye igitero cabwo ku gihugu ciwe
 Ku bwa Zelensky, imfashanyo ya gisirikare Amerika iha Ukraine si ubutabazi, ahubwo ni umutahe ku mutekano wa kazoza
 Ateye aka kamo mu gihe hari ibimenyetso ko imfashanyo ya Amerika ishobora kwihwezwa cane n’abo mu mugambwe w’Abarepubulika mu nama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka
 Ariko Perezida Biden yiyemeje gushigikira Ukraine “mu gihe cose bizoba nkenerwa”
 Biden yaremereye ico gihugu iyindi mfashanyo y’imiriyaridi zibiri z’amadorari, aca yiyemeza ko hazoboneka n’iyindi y’imiriyaridi 45 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika
 Mu kiganiro rusangi n’abamenyeshamakuru, Perezida Biden yavuze ko ata mpungenge namba afise zo gukomeza urunani mpuzamahanga
 Mu gihe hari amakenga ko bimwe mu bihugu bicuditse na Amerika bishobora kuba vyumva biruhishijwe n’iyi ntambara n’ingorane z’imfungurwa be n’igitoro kw’isi, umukuru w’igihugu ca Amerika avuga ko ashima cane ingene bafatanye mu nda mu gushigikira Ukraine
 Nk’incuti ikomeye ya Ukraine, Amerika imaze guha ico gihugu gihanganye n’Uburusiya imiriyaridi 50 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika nk’imfashanyo y’ubutabazi n’umutekano – isumba kure cane iy’igihugu kindi ico ari co cose
 Perezida Zelensky – ari mu mwambaro w’intambara usanzwe umuranga, ugizwe n’agapira gasa n’urwatsi n’ibirato vy’intambara – yavuze ko yizeye ko inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka zizokwemeza imfashanyo y’inyongera y’imiriyaridi 45 z’amadorari y’Abanyamerika - ubu ikaba iri imbere y’inama nshingamateka – kugira ngo “idufashe kurwanira agateka n’ubwigenge vyacu”
 Abarepubulika – mu gihe biteze gufata uburongozi bw’inama nshingamateka mu kwa mbere – baragabisha ko batazopfa kwemera vyose kuri Ukraine
 Mu vy’ukuri, ugushaka kw’Abarepubulika mu gufasha Ukraine kugenda kugabanuka
 Mu mwihwezo wakozwe mu kw’icumi na rimwe, inusu y’abanywanyi b’umugambwe w’Abarepubulika nibo bashigikiye ko Ukraine ibandanya ihabwa imfashanyo – ikaba yakorotse kuva ku rugero rwa 80% mu kwa gatatu
 Ariko, Perezida Zelensky - yashitse muri Amerika ari mu ndege y’igisirikare ca Amerika kirwanira mu kirere avuye mu gisagara ca Rzeszow  muri Pologne -  avuga ko “n’aho mu nama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka himirije impinduka”, yizeye ko imigambwe yompi izoshigikira igihugu ciwe
