Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine  avuga ko ari mu nzira aja  i Washington kuri uyu wa gatatu, aho aza kubonana na Perezida Joe Biden wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika
 Ni rwo urugendo  rwiwe rwa mbere agize hanze y’igihugu kuva igitero c’Uburusiya gitanguye mu kwa kabiri
 Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu wa Amerika) iremeza uru rugendo, ikavuga kandi ko izoha Ukraine misire zo mu bwoko bwa Patriot, zizokwongerereza  cane iki gihugu ubushobozi bwo gukingira ikirere
 Zelensky kandi ategekanya gushikiriza ijambo inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka zikoranye yongere agire n’amanama atari make
 Yanditse kuri Twitter ati: “Ndi mu nzira nja muri Amerika mu ntumbero yo gukomeza ubushobozi bwa Ukraine bwo kwihagararako no kwivyukiranya, hamwe no kwivuna abansi”
 Perezida Zelensky arakunze kwakira abategetsi mvamakungu ku mugwa mukuru Kyiv, kandi abandanya agendera ingabo ziri ku rugamba muri Ukraine
 Perezida Zelensky arakunze kandi kuvugana n’abategetsi b’isi kuri terefone no ku buhinga bwa videwo – akenshi ari mu biro iwe i Kyiv
 Ariko urugendo rutamenyeshejwe mu gihugu co hanze rubaye urwa mbere kuva intambara itanguye, kandi rukerekana akamaro k’imigenderanire ya Ukraine na Amerika isanzwe iri kw’isonga mu gutanga imfashanyo ya gisirikare
 Mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru imbere y’urugendo rwa Zelensky, Maison Blanche yemeje iyindi mfashanyo mu rwego rw’umutekano ifise agaciro k’imiriyaridi zababa zibiri z’amadorari y’abanyamerika
 Muri yo harimwo misire zo mu bwoko bwa Patriot, zizofasha Ukraine gukingira ibibanza nyamukuru ibitero vy’Uburusiya
 Abategetsi bamaze igihe basaba Uburengero ibirwanisho bigezweho vyo gukingira ikirere
 Uburusiya bumaze igihe butera ibigo vy’amasoko ntanganguvu, ivyatumye amamiriyoni y’abanyagihugu bisanga mu kizime muri kino gihe c’ubukonje burenze urugero
 Maison Blanche ivuga ko izokwigisha ingabo za Ukraine ingene bakoresha izi misire za Patriot, kandi ko “bizofata igihe kanaka”
 Hari ibikorwa biriko birabandanya muri kino gihe muri Amerika vyo gusaba ko hemezwa integuro y’itegeko ryoha Ukraine imiriyaridi zirenga 40 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika nk’imfashanyo y’inyongera  imbere y’umwaka wa 2023
  Ku bijanye n’amafaranga akoreshwa muri rusangi mu mfashanyo ya gisirikare kuva intambara itanguye, Amerika imaze gutanga imiriyaridi 18,5 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika, imfashanyo isumba kure cane iyitangwa n’ikindi gihugu ico ari co cose
 Perezida Zelensky asaba ayandi mafaranga, akavuga ko ku kwezi Ukraine ikoresha hafi imiriyaridi zitanu z’amadorari mu vya gisirikare
 Akoze uru rugendo inyuma y’umusi umwe agize urugendo rutamenyeshejwe mu gisagara kiri mu ntambara ca Bakhmut, aho ingabo za Ukraine n’iz’Uburusiya zimaze amezi atari make mu ntambara zikomeye
 Ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu bimenyesha ko yabonanye n’ingabo yongera atanga n’udushirukabute ku basirikare
 Uru rugendo rwari intambwe ikomeye yo kwerekana ko adatinya urukamvye – be no kwerekana ko afashe mu mugongo ingabo za Ukraine zihanganye n’umwansi muri zimwe mu ntambara zikomeye cane muri zino ndwi za vuba
 Abasirikare bahaye Zelensky ibendera rya Ukraine ririko amazina yabo bamusaba ko yorishikiriza Perezida Biden n’inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka za Amerika, nk’uko vyabonetse muri kamera (camera)
 Kuri uwo musi nyene, ari muri Kremlin, Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya yahaye ibidari abasirikare bagize uruhara mu gitero c’Uburusia kuri Ukraine
