 Hagati aho, ivyo biharuro ntibirimwo abateshejwe izabo ariko bakaguma muri Ukraine

Aba Taliban babujije abagore kwiga amakaminuza muri Afghanistan, ingingo yiyamirizwa n’amakungu mbere yateye n’umwikomo mu rwaruka muri ico gihugu
 Umushikiranganji w’inyigisho za kaminuza yatangaje iyo ngingo isubiza inyuma igihugu ejo ku wa kabiri, avuga ko yategerezwa guca ija mu ngiro ubwo nyene
 Iyo ngingo ije gusubiza inyuma gusumba indero ku bagore -  mu gihe abakobwa bari bamaze kubuzwa kwiga amashure yisumbuye kuva aba Taliban bagarutse ku butegetsi mu mwaka uheze
 Kuno uno wa gatatu, hari abagore bamwe bateguye imyiyerekano ku mugwa mukuru Kabul Abagore bahurikiye mw’ishirahamwe Afghanistan Women's Unity and Solidarity bavuga bati: “Uno musi twihaye amabarabara ya Kabul kugira ngo twerekane akababaro kacu ku ngingo yo kwugara amashure ya kaminuza ku bakobwa”
 Ariko iyi myiyerekano yarimwo abantu bake yatujijwe vuba bwango n’abategetsi b’aba Taliban
 Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU n’ibihugu bitari bike biriyamiriza iri tegeko, risubiza inyuma Afghanistan nko mu gihe c’ubutegetsi bwa mbere bw’aba Taliban igihe abakobwa batari bemerewe kwiga amashure
 Intumwa idasanzwe ya ONU muri Afghanistan avuga ko ari "iyindi ntambwe inyuma isubiriye guhonyanga uburenganzira bwo kwiga kuri bose ibandanya irondera gufuta abagore mu mibereho ya Afghanistani”
 Ku ruhande rwayo, Amerika iriyamiriza bikomeye ingingo z’aba Taliban, ikavuga ko iyo ngingo "izogira ingaruka mbi ku ba Taliban”
 Mw’itangazo, umunyamabanga wa reta ajejwe imigenderanire wa Amerika, Antony Blinken , avuga ati: "Aba Taliban ntibizere ko bashobora kwinjira mu muryango mpuzamakungu igihe cose batazoba barubahiriza uburenganzira bw’abanya-Afghanistani bose
 "Nta gihugu gishobora gutera imbere mu gihe inusu y’abanyagihugu baco bakibohewe amaboko imugongo”
 I Kabul, abanyeshure b’abakobwa na bo nyene babwiye BBC akababaro kabo
 Umwe yiga kuri kaminuza ya Kabul agira ati: "Barasambuye ikiraro conyene compuje na kazoza kanje
 "None nogira gute? Nari nizeye ko nari kwiga ngahindura kazoza kanje canke bikambera umuco mu buzima bwanje, ariko bagisambuye”
 Uwundi nawe yabwiye BBC ko ari “umugore yatakaje vyose”
 Yahoze yiga amategeko ya Islam, Sharia – akavuga ko amabwirizwa y’aba Taliban ateye kubiri “n’uburenganzira Islam na Allah baduhaye”
 Abwira BBC ati: “Ni ngombwa ko baja mu bindi bihugu vya ki-Islam kugira ngo babone ko ibikorwa vyabo atari ivya Islam”
 Ibihugu vy’uburengero bimaze umwaka wose bisaba aba Taliban gukomeza indero y’abagore nimba bashaka kwemerwa ku mugaragaro nka reta ya Afghanistan
 Hagati aho, mu gihugu kibanyi ca Pakistan, umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire yavuze ko ababajwe n’iyi ngingo y’aba Taliban
 Bilawal Bhutto Zardari  ati: "Ndacibaza ko inzira yoroshe kugira dushike ku ntumbero yacu – n’aho hari inzitizi nyinshi ku nyigisho y’abagore no ku bindi – ni uguca kuri Kabul no kuri reta mfatakibanza”
 Aba Taliban bari bemereye abanyagihugu ubutegetsi bugenza buhoro inyuma y’aho bafatiye ubutegetsi mu mwaka uheze inyuma y’aho Amerika itahukaniye ingabo zayo
 Ariko Aba ba-Islam bagendera ku vyiyumviro bikaze vya Islam babandanije basubiza inyuma uburenganzira bw’abagore n’ubwigenge mu gihugu
 Umutegetsi w’aba Taliban Hibatullah Akhundzada n’abo bafatanije kurongora igihugu ntibigeze berekwa indero igezweho yo mu mashure – canecane ku bakobwa n’abagore
 Bamwe mu bategetsi biyoroheje ntibashigikiye iyi ngendo, abahinga bakavuga ko iki kibazo cabacanishijemwo muri uno mwaka wose
 Hamwe n’ivyo, ejo ku wa kabiri ubushikiranganji bw’indero bwavuze ko abahinga babwo bihweje intunganyo y’ivyigwa vya kaminuza n’uburyo bigamwo, hanyuma bafata ingingo ko abakorwa bahagarikwa vy’agateganyo “gushika hatunganijwe uburyo bwiza”
 Buvuga kandi ko vuba buzotanga iyo nteguro kandi ko “abanyagihugu batogira ubwoba”

 Hagati aho, mu kwa gatatu, aba Taliban bari bemeye gusubira kwugurura amashure yisumbuye amwe amwe y’abakobwa ariko mu nyuma barabihagarika ku musi nyene bari biteze gusubira kw’ishure
 Iri totezwa kandi rikurikiye urukurikirane rw’ayandi mabwirizwa yo gukumira abagore mu mezi aheze
 Mu kw’icumi na rimwe, abagore barabujijwe kuja mu bibanza vy’ihuriro, mu mazu y’ukwinonora imitsi hamwe no mu bwogero rusangi ku mugwa mukuru
 Umwigisha wa kaminuza akongera akaba n’umwe mu banya Afghanistan baharanira uburenganzira bwa kiremwamuntu avuga ko aba Taliban barangije ingingo yabo yo gutaramura abagore mu kubabuza amashure kaminuza
 Humaira Qaderi  yabwiye BBC ati: "Iki ni co kintu ca nyuma aba Taliban bari basigaje gukora
 Afghanistani si igihugu ku  bagore, ahubwo ni ikirunduru ku bagore”
 Hari haciye amezi atatu aba Taliban bemereye ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’abakobwa n’abagore gukora ikibazo co kwinjira muri kaminuza hafi mu ntara zose z’igihugu
 Ariko hariho ivyigwa batari bemerewe gusaba kwiga, aho nk’ivyigwa vy’ubufundi, ubutunzi, ubuganga bw’ibitungwa n’uburimyi vyari bibujijwe, mugihe kandi ivyigwa vy’ukumenyesha amakuru bibujijwe cane rwose
 Imbere y’iyi ngingo y’ejo ku wa kabiri, amashure kaminuza yari yamaze gushiraho amategeko akumira abagore kuva aba Taliban bafashe ubutegetsi mu 2021
 Hari ubwinjiriro n’amasomero bitandukanye ufatiye ku gitsina, kandi abanyeshure b’abakobwa bategerezwa gusa kwigishwa n’abigisha b’abagore canke abagabo bashaje
 Ubutunzi bwa Afghanistani ahanini bugendera ku mfashanyo mpuzamakungu kuva mu myaka mirongo iheze, ariko amashirahamwe y’abagiraneza hamwe hamwe yagabanije - ariko ahandi arakuraho burundu -    imfashanyo yatanga mu gisata c’indero inyuma y’aho aba Taliban bankiye kwemerera abakobwa kwiga amashure yisumbuye
 Abigisha benshi barataye baromoka inyuma y’aho ingabo zari zirongowe na Amerika ziviriye muri ico gihugu, nayo muri uno mwaka abigisha benshi bakaba baramaze amezi atari make badahembwa

Ukraine iriko irongereza inguvu ku rubibe ihana na Biélorussie/Belarus kubera ubwoba ifise ko Uburusiya bufise kuba buriko burategura ikindi gitero, nk’uko bivugwa n’umutegetsi wo muri reta
 Icegera c’umushikiranganji w’intwaro yo hagati Yevhen Yenin yabwiye BBC ko Ukraine ishobora kuba iriko iratsimbataza umutekano ku rubibe na Biélorussie mu kwongereza ingabo n’ibirwanisho
 Iyi nkuru ije inyuma y’aho Vladimir Putin agendeye Minsk (umugwa mukuru wa Biélorussie) kubonana na Perezida Alexander Lukashenko w’iki gihugu
 Biélorussie isangiye urubibe n’Uburusiya hamwe na Ukraine
 Mu nyuma, umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yategetse gutsimbataza umutekano ku mbibe z’Uburusiya n’ukugenzura ingene abanyagihugu babayeho hagati mu Burusiya
 Avuga ko inzego z’umutekano zitegerezwa gutuza vuba bwango ikintu ico ari co cose cogerageza kuvogera imbibe z’Uburusiya, kurwanya icoza kigomba guhungabanya umutekano kivuye hanze, kandi zikamenya ivyitso n’abatovyi
 Yavuze kandi ko inzego zidasanzwe zijejwe umutekano zitegerezwa gucungera umutekano w’uturere twa Ukraine Moscou (umugwa mukuru w’Uburusiya)  ivuga ko ari rwayo
 Mu turere tumwe tumwe muri utu, cane cane Kherson, ingabo z’Uburusiya ziherutse gutakaza bikomeye
 Umusikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi w’Uburusiya atangaza ko ingabo zabwo ziri muri Biélorussie zigiye gukorana imyimenyerezo rusangi n’iza Biélorussie
 Avuga kuri ibi no kuri uru rugendo, Yenin yemeza ati: "Turiko turakomeza ibirindiro vyo kwivuna umwansi ku rubibe n’Uburusiya hamwe na Biélorussie”
 Mu gihe Biélorussie itaragira uruhara muri ino ntambara mu buryo bweruye, yaremereye ingabo z’Uburusiya gukoresha ubutaka bwayo igihe butangura iki gitero mu kwa kabiri
 Minsk ibandanya iterwa akamo na Moscou ko yofata mu mugongo gusumba “iki gikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare”
 Ariko umuvugizi wa Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya) Dmitry Peskov arahakana aya makuru, akavuga ko ari “irementanya ry’ubujuju ridafise ishingiro”
 Perezida Putin yarashitse i Minsk mu biganiro na Perezida Lukashenko – bukaba ari bwo bwa mbere aba bategetsi babiri bahurira muri Biélorussie mu kiringo c’imyaka itatu n’inusu
 Uwu mubonano ufatwa ko ari “urugendo rw’akazi” ukaba wamaze ikiringo c’amasaha arenga abiri
 Mu kiganiro rusangi n’abanyamakuru, Perezida Putin yavuze ko Uburusiya butashaka “kwigarurira” igihugu na kimwe
 Yavuze kandi ko “abansi” batazwi bashatse kubuza Uburusiya kwishira hamwe na Biélorussie
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu masaha yitereye yo ku wa mbere, umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bwa Amerika bujejwe imigenderanire, Ned Price yavuze ko ijambo rya Putin “ryuzuye uburyarya” kubera iki gihe yashaka kwigarurira Ukraine

Umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire w’Ubuhindi avuga ko igihugu ciwe congereje abasirikare ku rubibe gihana n’Ubushinwa ku rugero rutari bwigere rubaho
 Jaishankar yongerako y’uko Ubuhindi budashobora kwemera ko Ubushinwa “buhindura uko bwishakiye” uko ibintu bimeze ku mupaka
 Ashikirije aya majambo yiwe inyuma y’imisi mikeya ingabo z’Ubuhindi n’iz’Ubushinwa zikozanijeko mu karere ko ku rubibe gateje impari mu ntara ya Arunachal Pradesh
 Ubuhindi buvuga ko vyose vyatanguye igihe ingabo z’Ubushinwa zivogera ubutaka bwabwo
 Ubushikiranganji bw’Ubushinwa bujejwe imigenderanire buvuga ko ku vyo buzi, ibintu “bimeze neza muri rusangi ku mupaka” kandi ko impande zompi zibandanya ziganira kuri iki kibazo
 Ubuhindi n’Ubushinwa bisangiye urubibe rurangwa n’induru rungana na 3
440km – ruzwi nka Line of Actual Control, or LAC – rutaboneka neza
 Abasirikare bo ku mpande zompi bakunze gushamirana mu turere tutari duke, mbere icuka kibi rimwe rimwe kirarenga inkombe gushika n’aho batana mu mitwe
 Impande zompi ziragerageza kugarukana icuka ciza inyuma y’imishamirano yadutse mu kwa gatandatu 2020 mu Kiyaya ca Galwan (Galwan Valley) mu karere ka Ladakh amaja mu burengero – abasirikare 20 b’Ubuhindi hamwe n’abo Ubushinwa nibura bane bakaba barapfiriye mu ntambara
 Imishamirano iheruka – iya mbere mu kiringo kirenga umwaka -  ni iyabaye ku wa 09 Kigarama (12), ikaba yatumye abasirikare bakomereka bukebuke
 Impande zompi zaciye ziva muri ako karere, nk’uko igisirikare c’Ubuhindi cavuze
 Jaishankar yavuze ibi mu gihe yariko yishura ibibazo kuri iki kibazo mw’ijambo ryiwe yashikirije mu birori vyateguwe n’ikompanyi y’ibinyamakuru India Today ku wa mbere
 Ati: "Uno musi, igisirikare c’Ubuhindi carungitse ingabo zitari bwigere zirungikwa ku rubibe rw’Ubushinwa
 Uno musi igisirikare c’Ubuhindi carungitswe kuzibira Ubushinwa mu gihe bwogerageza guhindura intunganyo y’icungera ry’urubibe”
 Ubushinwa ntaco burishura kuri ibi
 Imishamirano iheruka yateje imvururu za poritike mu Buhindi mu ndwi iheze, aho imigambwe itavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi yivmbuye mu nama nshingamateka inyuma y’icipfuzo cayo c’ibiganiro ku kibazo co ku mupaka cankiwe
 Rahul Gandhi, umukuru w’umugambwe mukuru utavuga rumwe mu Buhindi Congress party, yagiriza reta kwirengagiza ibibazo biterwa n’Ubushinwa, akavuga kandi ko ingabo z’iki gihugu ”zikubita” iz’Ubuhindi ku rubibe
 Ari imbere y’inama nshingamateka ejo ku wa mbere, umushikiranganji Jaishankar yavuze ko amajambo ya Gandhi "ateza urubwa" abasirikare b’Ubuhindi anahakana ko reta itigira sindabibazwa ku biriko biraba
 "Nimba turi ba sindabibazwa ku Bushinwa, ni nde yarungitse igisirikare c’Ubuhindi ku rubibe? Nimba turi ba sindabibazwa ku Bushinwa, kubera iki turiko duhatira Ubushinwa ko igabanya icuka kibi kandi ikigiza inyuma ingabo”

