Afrika izotsindira igikombe c’isi yose “mu myaka 15-20”, niko umumenyereza w’umurwi nserukiragihugu wa Maroc Walid Regragui avuga, akaba ari na we mumenyereza wa mbere wa Afrika ahatswe gushika kuri iyo ntumbero
 Barongowe na Regragui, Les Lions de l'Atlas, babaye umurwi wa mbere wo ku mugabane wa Afrika ushitse mu gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi, aho bagiye gukurwamwo n’Ubufaransa buhejeje ihiganwa muri mu kibanza ca kabiri
 Uyu mumenyereza w’imyaka 47 yizeye ko Afrika izoronka akarusho mu myaka iri imbere, aho izoba iserukirwa n’ibihugu birenga bitanu ku ncuro ya mbere kuva mu 2026 no kubandanya
 Regragui ati: "Mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi kiri imbere, tuzoba dufise ibibanza icenda, ibi bikazodufasha kwiga gusumba
 "Mu myaka 15-20, ndazi neza ko umurwi wa Afrika uzotsindira igikombe
 Kuko igihe cose tuzokwama tuhigira vyinshi, rero urwaruka rwacu ruzoba rufise mu maraso igikombe c’isi”
 Kuva mu 1994, Afrika iserukirwa n’ibihugu bitanu – ibibanza bike cane ugereranije na 13 vya Bulaya, ikaba isumvya ikibanza kimwe Amerika y’ubumanuko isanzwe ifise ibihugu bike cane rwose, ikanganya na Aziya (iyo itaramutse yakira igikombe)
 Nyamara iki giharuro kuri Afrika kizokwiyongera hafi incuro zibiri  mbere gishobore gushika no kw’icumi mu gihe hogira igihugu cayo corengana inkino mpuzamigabane za play-off /barrage zo guhiganira ibibanza vy’abazokwitaba ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi
 Uyu mugabane ntiworoherwa gushika muri ca gice co gukuranamwo, aho mu 2018 ata murwi n’umwe washoboye gushikayo,  igihe cose ikama iserukirwa n’umwe gusa urengana inkino z’amatsinda kuva mu 1994 wongererejwe igitigiri, kiretse mu 2014 na 2022, aho imirwi ibiri ari yo yashoboye kurengana
 Uyo yahoze akinira umurwi nserukiragihugu wa Maroc avuga ati: "Ingorane zacu nk’imirwi ya Afrika, ntarinze kunegura cane, ni uko dufise ibibanza bitanu gusa, rero ibi bigasigura ko muri kino gihe Misiri itari kubamwo, canke Nigeria, Afrika y’Epfo, Mali, n’ibindi
 "Rero, igihe cose, kubera twama duhanganye (mu kurondera itike), ntivyoroshe na gato (gushobora kwigira ku gikombe c’isi)”
 Inyuma y’aho itsindiwe na Croatia mu rukino rwo kurondera ikibanza ca gatatu ku wa gatandatu, yama iheza iri mu bibanza vya mbere mu mahiganwa atandatu y’igikombe c’isi imaze gukina, Regragui avuga ko bari kuri urwo rugero kubera bobo bama baja muri aya mahiganwa
 Uyu mugabo yatsindiye ihiganwa ry’imirwi yabaye iya mbere ku mugabane wa Afrika mu ntango z’uno mwaka agira ati: "(Jose) Mourinho – igihe yari muri Manchester United – yaravuze ivyerekeye ADN/DNA y’uyo murwi, ariko ndibaza ko ikintu nk’iki kibaho no mu mirwi nserukirabihugu”
 "Kubera iki igihe cose imirwi ya Bulaya (yama ishika mu nkino za nyuma z’igikombe c’isi)? Croatia – kubera iki badutsinze bakarangiza ihiganwa bari mu kibanza ca gatatu? Ni uko bamenyereye cane izi nkino, igihe cose bama baronka itike yo kuja mu gikombe c’isi yose
 "Iyo wama witabira buri higanwa ry’igikombe c’isi, ukama ukina izi nkino igihe cose, zirakwigisha, abakinyi bakiri bato barahigira vyinshi
 Ibi bituma mw’ihiganwa rikurikira aba bakinyi bakiri bato bazosubirayo bakomeye cane”
 Inyuma y’imyaka 20, Maroc yagarutse mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi mu 2018, isubira uno mwaka, ibitari bwigere bibaho ko yikurikiranya uku kuva aho iherukira mu 1994-1998
 Muri Qatar, Maroc yateye intambwe zidasanzwe n’aho yahuye n’imirwi y’ibihangange kw’isi: Ububirigi (2), Espagne (7), Portugal (9), ikongera kandi, mu nkino zo mu matsinda, igaca imbere Croatia yari yahejeje ari iya kabiri mu 2018
 Umumeyereza wa Maroc yongerako ati: "Twaharonkeye inyigisho z’imyaka myinshi iyo uronse akaryo ko guhura na Croatia incuro zibiri mw’ihiganwa rimwe, igihugu kiza mu kibanza ca gatatu kw’isi”
 "Gukina na Espagne, Portugal, Ubufaransa, Ububirigi, na Canada, ni ibintu bidasanzwe – inkino zose zikomeye”
 Inyuma yo kwinjizwa igitsindo kimwe gusa mu nkino zitanu za mbere muri Qatar, mu nyuma vyahavuye vyanka kuri Maroc igihe itsinzwe n’Ubufaransa 2-0 mu nkino z’igice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma ku wa gatatu, imbere y’uko itsindwa na Croatia 2-1 ku wa gatandatu
 N’aho Regragui yababaye cane kubona Maroc itashoboye kuba umurwi wa mbere wa Afrika wari kuba ushitse mu rukino rwa nyuma canke ngo uhereze mu kibanza ca gatatu, ariteze ko intambwe idasanzwe umurwi wiwe washitseko igiye kwibonekeza ubu bwa vuba
 Ati: "Turababaye, ariko ni twikangura tuzomenya neza igikorwa kidasanzwe twashitseko
 "Inyuma y’uru rukino rwa nyuma, tuzokwihweza ngene ibintu vyagenze, ndazi ko tuzosanga Maroc yakoze ibintu bikomye cane
 Ubu rero, ndazi ko dufise igikorwa kidasanzwe imbere yacu”
 Uyu mumenyereza yiteze neza ko n’iyindi mirwi ikomakomeye y’umugabane nayo nyene igiye gukurikiranirwa hagufi muri kazoza
 "Ubu hagiye kuba vyinshi vyitezwe ku yindi mirwi ya Afrika irondera gushika ku vyo twashitseko
 "Maroc irerekanye ko (imirwi ya Afrika) ishoboye kandi itari kure cane (y’imirwi y’ibihangange), rero itandukaniro hagati y’imirwi ya Bulaya n’iya Afrika ni rito cane gusumba uko vyahoze, kandi ni utuntu duto cane
 “Ibi bigiye gutera intege umupira w‘amaguru muri Afrika”

Vyitezwe ko Ubuholande busaba imbabazi ku bucakara, biciye mw’ijambo riza gushikirizwa n’umushikiranganji wa mbere ari kumwe n’abandi bashikiranganji mu rugendo barimwo muri Caraibes na Suriname kuri uno wa mbere
 Ariko hari abanegura itariki iki gikorwa kiberako n’uburyo itangazo ryateguwe, ibi bikerekana ko ivyo Mark Rutte yateguye kuvuga bitaramenyekana
 Abamunegura bavuga ko hatabaye uguhanuza guhagije, bakavuga ko uravye ingene vyemejwe n’inama y’abashikiranganji y’Ubuholande harimwo “agatima k’ubukoloni”
 Amashirahamwe atandatu yo muri Suriname yasavye sentare ko yigiza imbere iyi ngingo yo gusaba imbabazi gushika ku wa 01 Mukakaro (7) 2023, itariki izohimbarizwako imyaka 150  izoba irangiye ubucakara buciwe mu bihugu vyahoze bitwarwa gikoloni n’Ubuholande
 DJ Etienne Wix, arongoye iradiyo mArt iri mu mashirahamwe asaba ko hagenwa itariki yindi, avuga ati:  "Nimba hari ivyo gusaba imbabazi, bikwiye kuba ku wa 01 Mukakaro, itariki y’ubwigenge bwacu, igihe badukurako iminyororo”
 Abanyafrika n’abanya-Asia barenga 600
000 baragurishijwe mu nzira ya magendo n’abacuruzi  b’abanya-Holande  hagati y’ibinjana vya 17 na 19
 Abagabo, abagore n’abana batwawe mu bucakara bakoreshejwe ku nguvu mu mirima y’ibikaju, ikawa n’itabi, mu kwimba ubutare abandi nabo bagirwa abacakara bo mu nzu “mw’isi nshasha”, ibihugu bwatwarwa gikoloni muri Amerika no mu mazinga ya Caraibes
 Barakorewe amabi atagira izina yo ku mubiri, ku mutima n’ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina
 Amafaranga yavuye muri iri koreshwa ry’ubugome yateje imbere ubwamwi bw’Ubuholande anagira uruhara mu kizwi nk’ “igihe c’inzahabu (Age d’Or/ Golden Age ), igihe caranzwe n’iduga ry’ubutunzi rikomeye mu kinjana ca 17 ari naho Ubuholande bwateye imbere cane mu rwego rw’ubuhinga n’imico
 Mu ntara ya Holland yonyene iri mu burengero, icigwa c’ikigo c’Ubuholande kijejwe ubushakashatsi, Dutch Research Council, cerekana ko ibice 40% vy’iduga ry’ubutunzi hagati ya 1730 na 1780 vyavuye ku bucakara
 "Ubuholande ni kimwe mu bihugu vya Bulaya bifise uruhara mu bucakara”, bivugwa na Pepijn Brandon, umwigisha wa kaminuza kuri kahise k’utunzi n’imibereho kw’ishure kaminuza Free University of Amsterdam, ari nawe yasohoye ubu bushakashatsi
 Abona ko mu myaka cumi iheze habaye impinduka ku kungene abanyagihugu batahura ubucakara bwakozwe n’Ubuholande, aho babona ko ubukoloni n’ubucakara vyari vyo shingiro ry’Ubuholande nk’igihugu cari imbere y’ibindi vyose mu bucuruzi kw’isi
 Avuga kandi ko ukungene iki kibazo citaweho mu binyamakuru no mu mashure vyerekana ko ubu ikibazo gifatwa mu buryo butandukanye cane
 Quinsy Gario ni umwe mu baharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu, avuga ati:  "Abantu hafi bose babona ko Igihe c’Inzahabu ari ijambo ribi, rero ikibazo nyamukuru si amajambo
 Nimba utahura ko Igihe c’Inzahabu kitakiri ic’inzahabu, none vyosigura iki kurondera kugorora ivyononekaye, ivyubatswe ico gihe”? Ico rero, nk’uko abivuga, nico categerezwa kuba intango yo gusaba imbabazi
 Imigambi yo gusaba imbabazi ije inyuma y’indwi hasohotse icegeranyo kivuga ko abantu bo mu bushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire y’Ubuholande babwirwa amajambo y’ivanguraruhu, mbere bamwe muri bo bakaba bashizwe ku ruhande mw’itangwa ry’ibibanza vyisumbuye kubera ibara ry’urukoba rwabo canke ubwoko bwabo
 Muri ico gisata nyene, ibihugu vya Afrika vyiswe “ibihugu vy’inguge” mu butumwa bahanahana hagati muri bo
 Vyabaye ngombwa ko ubu bushikiranganji buca busaba imbabazi, aho Wopke Hoekstra yemeye ko iki cegeranyo gishobora gutuma isura y’igihugu icafuka mu makungu
 Ubuholande buragirizwa ko bubandanya kandi bugakoresha ku mugaragaro ivanguraruhu mu bikorwa vyabwo
 Mu 2020, Tendayi Achiume, yaserukira ishirahamwe ONU mu gikorwa co kurwanya ivaguraruhu, yasanze ko ukwihanganira agakengere kwarazingamika utwigoro two kurwanya ikumira n’ivanguraruhu mu gipolisi c’Ubuholande
 Abanyagihugu bamuka ku bimukira bafise amazu matoya, bakaba abantu batize cane kandi badafise n’amikoro, babayeho nabi, nk’uko ikigo Statistics Netherlands kibitangaza
 Prof Brandon asigura ati: "Abimukira bafatwa nk’abanyagihugu bo hasi kuva bakiri bato
