 Ingingo imaze gutangazwa n’abacamanza bo muri Sentare Nkuru i Londres
 Ku butumwa kuri twitter, umushingamateka Caroline Lucas wo mu mugambwe wa Green  yavuze ko ari ngingo ”ibabaje cane”
  Yavuze ko umugambi wo kurungika bamwe mu barondera ubuhungiro mu Bwongereza ata ”bumuntu” igira, ”ntibereye kandi ntishobora gushirwa mu ngiro”
 Ariko abacamanza ivyo ntibabibona gutyo kuko bavuze ko uwo mugambi uhuye n’amategeko
 Sentare Nkuru yabaye irabangira gushika mu kwezi kwa Nzero (1) ku ngingo yerekeye kwemerera abashaka kwunguruza
  Umucamanza Lord Justice Lewis y avuze ati: “Twasanze bihuye n’amategeko ko reta ikora umugambi wo kurungika mu Rwanda abarondera ubuhungiro kugira dosiye zabo z’ubuhungiro zifatirwe  ingingo hariya
” Avuga ko ivyemezo vyashikirijwe sentare vyerekena ko integuro hagati y’Ubwomgereza n’Urwanda zigamije ku kurondera ko ama dosiye y’abasaba ubuhungiro yigirwa neza hariya
” Umucamanza yongeyeko ko uwo mugambi utarenga ku masezerano ya ONU agenga impunzi canke amategeko agenga uburenganzira bwa zina muntu
 Ariko yavuze ko ama dosiye y’abantu umunani barondera ubuhungiro atari yarihwejwe neza n’umushikiranganji ajejwe intwaro yo hagati igihe bari bafatiwe ingingo y’uko baba aba mbere barungikwa mu ndege ya mbere yari kubatwara mu Rwanda
 Ati: “Ayo ma dosiye azoshirwa ku ruhande hanyuma asubizwe ku mushikiranganji asubire kuyiga gushasha
” Umuvugizi muri reta y’Urwanda yakiriye neza ingingo ya sentare avuga ko Urwanda “rwiteguriye kwakira abarondera ubuhungiro no kubaha umutekano n’amahirwe yo  kwubaka ubuzima bushasha mu Rwanda”
 Umunyamakuru wa BBC Dominic Casciani akurikirana ibibazo vy’imbere mu Bwongereza n’amageteko avuga ko ingingo yafashwe n’abacamanza ari ikintu gikomeye cane ku mushikiranganji ajejwe intwaro yo hagati mu Suella Braverman n’uwo yasubiriye Priti Patel – hamwe rero no ku mushikiranganji wa mbere Rishi Sunak
 Kuko kuri bo,  izotuma vyoroha gusumba ko uwo mugambi, imnpera n'imperuka,  uja mu ngiro
 Ariko avuga ko atawokwibagirwa ko hazoba imanza nyinshi zo kwunguruza kuri iyo  ngingo y’uno munsi, mbere zishobora no gushika muri Sentare Ntahinyuzwa
 Ivyo navyo bizofata igihe
 Ariko ikiri co n’uko Sentare Nkuru -abacamanza babiri harimwo n’uwo muri sentare isubiramwo imanza – bavuze ko reta ifise  ububasha bw’amategeko bwo kurungika mu Rwanda abarondera ubuhungiro
 Reta y’Ubwongereza yakiriye neza iyo ngingo ya Sentare Nkuru
 Ivuga ko ifise ishaka rwo kurwanira umugamvbi wayo n’Urwanda mu gihe hari abaharanira ko uwo mugambi bishoboka ko bazokwunguruza
 Kubera ivyo umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bwa mbere yavuze ko ata kirangaminsi co kurungika indege za mbere  mu Rwanda yotanga
 Yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ati : “Dushaka kugenda vyihuse uko bishoboka kwose”
 Uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere, Boris Johnson, ari nawe reta yiwe yazanye uwo mugambi, yashimye cane ingingo ya Sentare Nkuru
 Yanditse kuri Twitter ko ari yo "nzira yonyene y'ubuntu yo guhangana n'ikibazo c'ubugome  bw'abantu barondera inyungu mu rudandazwa rwo kujabukana mu kinyegero abarondera ubuhungiro
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere w'ubu, Rishi Sunak, yavuze ati: "Twamye tuvuga ko uwo mugambi wacu wo mu Rwanda uhuye n'amategeko, nkaba ndyohewe n'uko vyemejwe uyu munsi
" Sunak yavuze ko "bitazokworoha" canke ngo  buno nyene ubuze ubwato bw'abaza kurondera ubuhungiro kubandanya bushika ku mucamo w'Ubwongereza, ariko yizeye ko azobishikako
 Ishirahamwe riharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Amnesty International  rivuga ko uwo mugambi ukwiye guhebwa
 Steve Valdez-Symonds, umuyobozi ajejwe impugnzi n’abarondera ubuhungiro mu Bwongereza  avuga ko “umugambi wo mu Rwanda ukwiye guhebwa wose uko wakabaye”
 Avuga ko iryo shirahamwe n’ubu rihagaritswe umutima n’uko uwo mugambi “ubangamiye cane amategeko mpuzamakungu agenga impunzi”
 Hagati aho, umuyobozi w’intumbero muri Croix Rouge yo mu Bwongereza, Christina Marriott, avuga ko “kurungika ahandi ibiremwamuntu” bidakwiye kuronka ikibanza mu ndinganizo y’Ubwongereza ku barondera ubuhungiro
 Avuga ko ata “kinini bizofasha kugira bibuze abantu gukora ibishobora gushira ubuzima bwabo mu kaga kugira bashike abo boronka umutekano
” Amashirahamwe y’abagiraneza,  Care4Calais na Dentention Action,   ni abiri ari mu mashirahamwe yarwanije uwo mugambi avuga ko uteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Yavuze ko ababajwe n’ingingo ya Sentare Nkuru yaciye urubanza ivuga ko uwo mugambi udateye kubiri n’amategeko, amenyesha ko agiye kwiyumvira kwunguruza
 Detention Action yarahiye kurwanya umugambi ivuga ko ”uhutaza kandi  ubabaza”

Na Marita Moloney BBC News Ukraine yagiriza Uburusiya ko buriko butegura igitero rutura co ku butaka mu ntango z’umwaka buca dutangura, n’aho igisirikare cabwo giherutse gutakaza ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky n’abategetsi bakuru baragabisha ko Kyiv n’incuti zayo badategerezwa kwijajara
 Intwazangabo nkuru mu gisirikare zivuga ko ico gitero gishobora kuba mu karere ka Donbas, mu bumanuko canke mbere gitera kija mu mugwa mukuru Kyiv
 Abihweza ibintu n’ibindi bo mu burengero bavuga ko ubushobozi bw’Uburusiya bwo gukora igitero co ku butaka kikagenda neza bugenda bugabanuka cane
 Muri ino ndwi, intwazangabo ikuriye igisirikare c'Ubwongereza Admiral Sir Tony Radakin yavuze ko intambara ishobora kugenda imera nabi kuri Moscou avuga ko ubu igenda ikehanirwa cane n’uburyo
 Mu rukurikirane rw’ibiganiro yagiye aha abanyamakuru, umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi, Oleksii Reznikov, avuga ko ivyemezo vyerekana ko Uburusiya butegura igitero gishasha gikomeye bigenda vyongerekana, n’aho buherutse gutakaza bikomeye ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Abona ko iki gitero gishobora kuba mu kwa kabiri igihe inusu y’abarikiri 300
000 Uburusiya bwinjije mu gisirikare mu kw’icumi kugira baje gufasha ku rugamba muri Ukraine bazoba bahejeje imyimenyerezo
 Reznikov yabwiye ikinyamakuru the Guardian ati: "Iyindi nusu ya kabiri, hafi 150
000…izokwitegura mu kiringo c’amezi hafi atatu
 Ibi bisigura ko bariko bagerageza gutangura ikindi gitero nko mu kwa kabiri nk’uko vyagenze mu mwaka uheze
 Izi nizo nteguro zabo”
 "Kremlin iriko igerageza kurondera ayandi mayeri y’ukungene yotsinda intambara”, niko avuga, akongerako y’uko yiteze ko Uburusiya bugiye guhamagara abandi banyagihugu kwinjira mu gisirikare
 Igitero gishasha ca Moscou gishobora kuba nko mu kwa mbere ariko cane cane mu gihe c’impeshi, nk’uko bivugwa n’ikinyamakuru the Economist, aho kivuga ko uyu ari umwihwezo wa Perezida Zelensksy, Jenerali Valery Zaluzhny na Jenerali Oleksandr Syrskyi mu biganiro baherutse gutanga
 Umukuru w’igisirikare ca Ukraine, Jenerali Zaluzhny avuga ati: "Abarusiya bariko bategura izindi ngabo nshasha zababa 200
000
 Nta nkeka mfise ko bazosubira bakagerageza gufata Kyiv”
 Avuga ko Uburusiya “buriko buritegura ijana kw’ijana”, akongerako y’uko “igikorwa nyamukuru kuri Ukraine…ari ugushiraho ingabo z’integabizoza ikitegurira intambara ishobora kuba mu kwa kabiri, ariko cane cane mu kwa gatatu, canke mbere no mu mpera z’ukwa mbere”
 Ati: "Ishobora kudatangurira muri Donbas, ariko igatera ija muri Kyiv, amaja muri Biélorussie/Belarus, ariko kandi kigashobora kuba amaja mu bumanuko”
 Impande zompi zanse agahengwe ka Noweli kandi nta biganiro vyo kurondera kurangiza intambara bihari
 Abahinga ba gisirikare bavuga ko igihe c’ubukonje gishobora guhagarika ibikorwa, n’aho  intambara zikomeye zibandanya, cane cane mu ntara ya Donetsk, aho Abarusiya bariko basatira kugira ngo bigarurire igisagara ca Bakhmut
 Ukraine yaratsimbataje igisata cayo kijejwe gukingira ikirere mu ntumbero yo guhangana n’ibisasu vya misire vy’Uburusiya, ifashijwe n’Uburengero, ariko ikaba ibandanya isaba ibindi birwanisho rutura
 Ejo ku wa kane, incuti zayo zo mu burengero zariyemeje kuyiha izindi mfashanyo z’amafaranga n’inyigisho za gisirikare
 Abategetsi b’umuryango w’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya bemeye kurekura imiriyarigi 18 z’ama-euro yo gufashisha Ukraine mu mwaka uza, no gufatira Moscou ibindi bihano ku ncuro igira icenda
 I Washington, igisirikare ca Amerika gitangaza ko kigiye kwigishiriza ingabo za Ukaine mu Budagi
 Kuva mu kwa mbere, ingabo 500 buri kwezi zizohabwa inyigisho, zizogenda ziyongera ku basirikare barenga 15
000 ba Ukraine bamaze kwigishwa na Amerika n’incuti zayo kuva mu kwa kane

Abantu batanu, harimwo Abarundi babiri, nibo bakomerekeye mu gitero c’igisasu ntezwantoke (grenade) cabereye mw’ikambi y’impunzi ya Dzaleka muri Malawi, nk’uko bitangazwa n’igipolisi c’ico gihugu
 Iki gitero cabaye ku wa gatatu kw’isaha imwe z’ijoro kw’isoko nkuru y’iyo kambi, nk’uko bimenyeshwa n’igipolisi, kikavuga kandi ko cahagaritse impunzi y’umunyarwanda yikekwa ko ari we yakoze ico gitero n’ibigirankana
 “Barabonye umuntu yakije umwampi imbere y’uko atera ikintu ciketswe ko yari grenade”, niko Gladson M'bumpha, umuvugizi w’igipolisi mu karere ka Dowa yabwiye BBC
 M'bumpha avuga ko muri aba batanu bakomeretse harimwo Butoyi Fideli arongoye impunzi z’Abarundi muri iyo kambi, hamwe kandi na Bruno Ndayishime, umunyamabanga wiwe
 Avuga ko muri kino gihe bataramenya imvo yatumye uyu muntu atera iyi grenade, ariko ko uwiketswe ariko arabazwa
 Gladson M'bumpha avuga ko iyo kambi  irwiriyemwo impunzi “z’Abarundi, Abanyarwanda n’Abakongomani”, ariko ko harimwo n’izindi ziva mu bihugu bitandukanye nka Tanzania na Somalia
 Avuga ko iki ari co gitero ca mbere kibaye muri ino kambi yo mu karere ka Dowa, kandi ko igipolisi kiriko kirakora ibishoboka vyose kugira ngo kimenye uwagirizwa igituma yateye grenade abo bantu
 Ati: “Iki ni ikintu catumye igipolisi kimera magabo kuko impunzi ntizemerewe gutunga ibirwanisho nk’ibi bicira umuriro”
 Avuga ko iyo kambi yari isanzwe itekanye imbere y’uko iki gitero kiba
 Umwe mu barundikazi barongoye abandi muri iyo kambi atashatse ko izina ryiwe rimenyekana, yabwiye BBC ko impunzi muri iyo kambi zifise ubwoba kuko ari ikintu kitari bwigere kibaho kuva iyo kambi itanguye
 Ati: “Ni ikintu caduteye ubwoba kuko cadushikiye giturumbuka kandi tudashobora gutahura ingene cashitse, ikintu tutari tumenyereye kubona mu nkambi y’impunzi mu myaka ishika 30 imaze”
 Avuga ko, n’aho uwikekwa gukora ico gitero ari impunzi y’umunyarwanda, “tubanye neza nta kibazo dufitaniye n’abanyarwanda turi kumwe mu nkambi”
 Hagati aho, uyu mupfasoni avuga ko bafise ubwoba ko reta ya Malawi ishobora kubafatira ingingo zitabashimisha
 Ati: “Tubaye mugihugu nk’abashitsi, si igihugu cacu, barashobora kutwiyumvira ukundi kuntu, bakerekana ko kumbure turi abicanyi, canke ibindi”
 Asaba reta gukora amatohoza yimbitse kugira ngo bamenye intandaro y’ico kibi maze bashobore guhumurizwa
 Abajijwe nimba ata mugambi bafise wo guhunguka nk’uko reta y’Uburundi ibatera akamo, uyo mupfasoni avuga ati: “Reta ni reta nyene kandi ivuga nka reta, umwe wese afise ivyo yagiye ahunga bitandukanye n’ivyo uwundi
 “Umwe wese ashobora kuvuga ati jewe aho navuye nshobora kuhasubira nta kibazo, uwundi nawe ati jewe sinohasubira kuko mfise ibibazo
 “Rero ako kamo reta itera, iragatera ariko kitabirwa n’uwubikeneye, kuko buri muntu wese afise ibibazo vyiwe vyatumye ahunga”

OMS ivuga ko n'ubu igihagaze hahandi nyene   inyuma y'aho Ubuhindi buvugiye ko imiti ine y'inkorora ifitaniye isano n'impfu z'abana muri Gambia yujuje ibisabwa igihe yapimwa muri ico gihugu
 OMS yari yasohoye  imburi mu kwezi kwa Gitugutu  (10) igira inama abacungera ibijanye n'imiti kudasubira kugurisha iyo miti inyobwa (Sirop/syrup) ikorwa na kompanyi yo mu Buhindi
 Umutegetsi wo muri reta y'Ubuhindi yabwiye BBC ko OMS "yahurudutse" mu kwagiriza iyo miti
 Ariko iryo shami rya ONU riraba amagara kw'isi ryavuze ko ryakoze ico rijejwe
 Umutegetsi wo muri OMS yabwiye BBC kuri email ati: "Inshingano za OMS n'ukuburira isi ku bishobora kubangama
 OMS ihagaze ku co yakoze
" OMS yongeyeko ko izo "sirop zibangamye kandi zidakwiye kuba mu muti n'umwe, na gato
 Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Mukakaro (kw'indwi) abategetsi muri Gambia babonye ko hari ukwiyongera mu gukomereka amafvyigo mu bana bafise munsi y'imyaka itanu
 Reta mu nyuma yavuze ko abana 69 bapfuye  biturutse kuri izo ngorane ku mafyigo
 Mu kwezi kwa Gitugutu (10) , OMS yavuze ko izo mpfu zishobnora kuba zifitaniye isano n'imiti y'inkorora inyobwa ine  ikorwa na Maiden Pharmaceuticals, kompanyi yo mu Buhindi
 OMS ivuga ko yapimye iyo miti - romethazine Oral Solution, Kofexmalin Baby Cough Syrup, Makoff Baby Cough Syrup na  Magrip N Cold Syrup - hanyuma igasanga yarimwo urugero rutemewe rwa diethylene glycol  na  ethylene glycol nk'ibihumanya"
 Diethylene glycol na ethylene glycol ni ubumara ku muntu kandi ishobora kwica umuntu ayifashe
 \n\nUbuhidi bwaciye buvuga ko bugiye gutohoza kuri iyi miti buca butegeka Maiden Pharmaceuticals guhagarika kuyikora mw'ihinguriro ryayo rikuru riri mu ntara ya Haryana iri mu buraruko
 Ku wa  13 Kigarama (12), Muganga  VG Somani, umugenduzi mukuru w'imiti mu Buhindi, yandikiye ikete OMS avuga ko ibipimo vyakozwe kur iyo miti muri laboratoire ya reta  vyerekanye ko iyo miti "itari ihumanijwe" n'ivyo OMS yavuze
 Yongeyeko ati: "Dukurkije ivyegeranyo vya laboratoire ya reta , ibipimo vyo gusuzuma kuri iyo miti yose uko ari ine vyatoye ko yari yujuje ibisabwa 
" Ivyerekanywe n'ibimo biriko birihwezwa kandi n'umugwi w'abahinga b'Abahindi
 Umujenama mukuru mu bushikiranganji bw'Ubuhindi bujejwe amakuru yabwiye BBC ko OMS "yahurudutse" mu kwagiriza ko iyo miti y'inkorora ko ariyo yateye impfu  z'abana
 Kanchan Gupta yavuze ko OMS yihuse kwemeza ibintu ata vyemeza vy'ubuhinga ifise
 Yoyo (OMS), ivuga ko "iyo abana bapfuye ku bwinshi bitewe n'indwara y'amayobera, kaba ari akaga bisigura ko OMS itegerezwa gufata ingingo  yihuta"
 OMS ivuga ko "Laboratoire zatumwe na OMS muri Ghana no muri Suisse zapimye izo sirop ziketswe muri Gambia hanyuma ziremeza ko harimwo urugero rurengeje rwa  ethylene glycol na  diethylene glycol," ikabandanya ivuga ko buno nyene yaciye imenyesha ivyavuyemwo abategetsi bo muri Gambia n'Ubuhindi, yongera ibimenyesha abategetsi ba Maiden Pharmaceutical
 Mw'ikete ryiwe, Muganga  Somani avuga ko uwo mugwi w'abahinga wasavye OMS  izindi nkuru zihariye zifasha kwemeza ko iyo miti ishobora kurwaza ariko ko gushika ubu utarayabwa
 Iryo kete ntiryavuga neza neza ico uwo mugwi wasaba ico ari co
 BBC irondeye ibiro vya Muganga  Somani, vyayibwiye kubariza mu bushikirnganji bw'Ubuhindi bujejwe amagara
 BBC yabwandikiye ngo bugire ico buvuze
 Ubuhindi buhingura ica gatatu c'imiti yo kw'isi, cane cane mu buryo bwa "generique"
 Mu Buhindi niho habarizwa amwe mu mahinguriro  y'imiti atera imbere ku muvuduko mununi cane, ico gihugu ubu kikaba gifatwa nka "farumasi (pharmacie) y'isi" ,kandi  nico ahanini gikora imiti ikoreshwa muri Africa

