 Wagner ivuga ko yari yinjiye ku bushake bwiwe imbere y’uko apfa ”nk’intwari”
 Zambia yasavye guhabwa insiguro zose z’ingene vyagenze
 Itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP ryasubiyemwo umwe mu muryango avuga ko ikiziga kizoca kijamwa mu buruhikiro rw’abapfuye kugira hakorwe isumwa ry’icamwishe hanyuma azoshingurwe
 Uwo munyeshure w'imyaka 23 wo mw'ishure kaminuza rya Moscow Engineering Physics yari mu gihano c'igipfungo c'imyaka icenda azira gufatanwa ibiyayuramutwe
 U﻿muryango wiwe ufise ibibazo vyinshi kuri urwo rupfu kandi wipfuza kuraba ko ikiziga ari iciwe
 N﻿yirenda yapfuye mu kwezi kw'icenda ariko Uburusiya bwabimenyesheje reta ya Zambia hagati mu kwezi kw'icumi na rimwe
 U﻿buserukizi bwa Zambia muri Ukraine bwasanze ikiziga ca Nyirenda cajanywe mu gisagara ca Rostov-on-Don kiri ku rubibe rwo mu bumanuko bw'Uburusiya  nk'uko vyamenyeshejwe n'umushikiranganji wa Zambia ajejwe imigenderanire Stanley Kakubo
 U﻿mushikiranganji Kakubo yagize ati: "Nk'umushikiranganji, jewe ubwanje nagumye mvugana, kandi nzoguma mvugana n'umuryango wabuze kugira bamenye ukuri kw'ido n'ido y'ingene uwabo yapfuye
" Se wiwe Edwin Nyirenda yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru rya Reuters ko u﻿wo munyeshure yariko arakora akazi asanzwe akora igihe atariko ariga, ko gutanga amakete igihe haza umuntu atamenye amuha ipaki irimwo ibiyayuramutwe
 S﻿e yagize ati: "Ntituzi" uwakuye umuhungu wanje mw'ibohero, anongerako ko umuryango gusa "waronse ubutumwa buvuye ku mugabo tutazi wo mu Burusiya yatubwiye ko hari icipfuzo umuhungu wacu yasize yanditse, kandi dutegerezwa kuja mu Burusiya"
 Z﻿ambia yahora irungika abanyeshure kwiga mu Burusiya ku mfashanyo y'ico gihugu, nk'uko vyari vyagenze kuri Nyirenda
 U﻿ko yarekuwe ava mw'ibohero ntibizwi, ariko Uburusiya bwaremereye umwidegemvyo bamwe mu banyororo mu gihe na bo bokwemera kugwana mu ntambara ibahuza na Ukraine
 M﻿u kwezi kw'icenda hari amasanamu y'ibanga yagiye ahabona yerekana abacangero b'umugwi Wagner bariko bararondera abanyororo baja kugwana muri Ukraine
 M﻿uri iyo video umukuru wa Wagner, Yevgeny Prigozhin yaragaragaye ariko aratanga amategeko y'intambara, nko kudahirahira ngo utoroke canke kudakora imibonano mpuzabitsina n'abagore bo muri Ukraine, hanyuma aca aha abo banyororo iminota itanu yo kwiyumvira nimba bashaka kuja kugwana
