 Igisirikare ca Ukraine kivuga ko cakoroye amadrone cumi ejo ku wa gatandatu, ariko ko ayandi atanu akaba yarashoboye gutera ibirindiro vy’amasoko ntanganguvu, ivyatumye abantu bababa imiriyoni 1
5 babura umuyagankuba
 Mu nyuma y’aho, umukuru w’igisagara ca Melitopol wo ku ruhande rwa Ukraine akaba yarahunze avuga ko hari igitero cakozwe kuri ico gisagara kiri mu minwe y’abarusiya
 Amasanamu yasohowe n’umutegetsi yashizweho n’Uburusiya yerekana urubeya runini rw’umuriro
 Igitero c’Uburusiya kuri ico gisagara ca Odesa kiri ku nyanja cakozwe n’amadrone ya Irani ku nyubakwa ikomeye, nk’uko abategetsi ba Ukraine babivuga
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe rya buri mugoroba yama acisha kuri videwo, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky  yaraye avuze ati: "Ibintu vyifashe nabi cane muri Odesa
 "Ikibabaje ivyo bitero vyari bikomeye, ibi bikazotuma dukenera umwanya kugira ngo tugarukane umuyagankuba
 Ntibisaba amasaha, ariko bizosaba imisi mikeya”
 Kuva mu kw’icumi, Moscou ibandanya itera ibibanza vy’amasoko ntanganguvu ikoresheje ibisasu vya misire n’ibitero vy’amadrone, ni inyuma y'aho ingabo za Vladimir Putin zitsindiwe  mu buryo buteye isoni mu bibanza bitari bike vya Ukraine
 Ku wa kane, Putin yariyemeje kubandanya ibitero ku bibanza vy’amasoko ntanganguvu vya Ukraine n’aho vyiyamirizwa n’amakungu, na rirya bisiga amamiriyoni y’abanyagihugu mu kizime
 I Melitopol, abategetsi begamiye kuri Moscou bavuga ko igitero ca misire cishe abantu babiri gikomeretsa abandi cumi , ni mu gihe Ivan Fedorov, umukuru w’igisagara ari mu buhungiro, avuga ko abatari bake “mu bateye igihugu” bishwe
 Mu butumwa yacishije ku rubuga rwa Telegram, Yevgeny Balitsky, buramatari w’intara ya Zaporizhzhia yagenywe n’Uburusiya avuga ati:  "Igisata kijejwe gucungera ibirere casambuye ibisasu vya misire bibiri, nayo bine bikaba ari vyo vyashitse aho vyatewe”
 Avuga kandi ko “ikigo c’iteramiro” ahari abantu bariko bivuna umusase, casenyuwe n’igitero ca Ukraine hakoreshejwe ibisasu vya misire vyo mu bwoko bwa Himars
 Oleksiy Arestovych, umuhanuzi wa Perezida Zelensky avuga ko Melitopol, igisagara kiri mu minwe y’Uburusiya kuva mu kwa gatatu, ari igisagara ngirakamaro mu gukingira ubumanuko
 Mu kiganiro kuri videwo ku mbuga hwaniro, Arestovych avuga ati: "Uburyo bwose buhabwa ingabo z’Uburusiya mu buseruko bw’intara ya Kherson gushika ku rubibe rw’Uburusiya hafi ya Mariupol niho bucishwa”
 “Mu gihe Melitopol yofatwa, umurongo wose wo kwivuna gushika muri Kherson woba ufashwe
 Ingabo za Ukraine zoba zironse inzira izishikana muri Crimea/ Crimée”
Na Chris Bevan BBC Sport ku kibuga Al Thumama Stadium, Doha Indoto za Cristiano Ronaldo zo gushobora gutsindira igikombe c’isi yose zirarangiye, kandi bisa n’uko ari ubutakigaruka – ariko none twovuga ko umwuga wiwe urangiye burundu? Aho ashiriwe ku rutonde rw’abasubirizi inyuma yo gushwana n’umumenyereza, urugendo rwa Ronaldo muri rino higanwa ntirwigeze ruboneka ko rwari guhava rurangira mu mahoro – ariko gusa amarira yagize inyuma y’’aho Portugal ikuriwe mw’ihiganwa yabaye incamake y’ingene ibintu bimeze ubu
 Inyuma yo gutsindwa na Maroc bisigura ko uyu mukinyi w’imyaka 37 gushika ubu ata mudari w’intsinzi y’igikombe c’isi yose agiye yambaye – agashimwe konyene agiye ataronse – mu gihe ubu ari ishusho kw’isi yose ariko idafise umurwi n’umwe yovuga iti ‘aha ni muhira’, inyuma y’aho aviriye muri Manchester United mu buryo atari bwiza, hari mu kwezi guheze
 Ico gihe abantu bari basanzwe bariko bibaza nimba yari gusubira gukinira umurwi wiwe, ubu naho, mu gihe abantu muri Portugal bakimukunda cane, hakaba hagiye gukurikira ibibazo kuri kazoza kiwe mu gihugu
 Ronaldo yavuye muri Man U hasigaye igihe gito ngo ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose ritangure, ariko Qatar yatanguye neza kuri we
 Igitsindo yinjije kuri penalty yateje impari mu rukino rwa mbere rwa Portugal mw’itsinda ryayo igihe ikina na Ghana cabaye ico “ubuhinga budasanzwe” ku bwa Fifa, kikaba camutumye yitwa umukinyi wa mbere yinjije mu mahiganwa atanu y’igikombe c’isi yose
 Ariko kuva ico gihe ibintu vyaciye bitangura kugenda nabi, mbere akaba atashoboye no kwinjiza igitsindo na kimwe mu nkino zibiri zakurikiye atanguzwa mu kibuga, imbere y’uko acanamwo n’umumenyereza  Fernando Santos inyuma y’aho amusubirije mu rukino rwabahuje na Korea y’Epfo
 Inyuma yo gushirwa ku ntebe y’abasubirizi mu rukino n’Ubuswisi mu gice c’umunani gishira ica nyuma – bukaba bwari bwo bwa mbere adatangujwe mu kibuga mu nkino zikomeye nk’izi kuva mu 2008 - umusore yamusubiriye Goncalo Ramos yateye bitatu wenyene, ubwo nyene Ronaldo aca yitwa igihangange co ku ntebe y’abasubirizi
 Ni nako yakinishijwe mu rukino rwa nijoro na Maroc, n’aho yahawe hafi igice ca kabiri cose, kuva ku munota wa 51, aho nyene igihugu ciwe camaze kurya kimwe ku busa
 Kuboneka mu kibuga vyonyene vyasiguye ko yari aciye uwundi muhigo  - urukino mpuzamakungu rwiwe rwa 196, aca anganya n’umusatirizi wa Koweit  Bader Al-Mutawa ku ruhande rw’abagabo – ariko nta kintu kinini yakoze ugereranije n’ivyo yagiye arakora mu myaka iheze
 Ronaldo yari asanzwe yaraciye umuhigo ku bitsindo vyinshi mu nkino mpuzamakungu ku ruhande rw’abagabo, aho afise 118, ariko ntiyigeze aboneka ko yari gushobora kwiyongera iteka imbere ya Maroc yaboneka ko yari yariye amavubi
 Ronaldo yashoboye gukora ku mupira incuro cumi gusa kandi vyamusavye ko akina gushika ku munota wa 91 kugira ngo ashobore gutera mw’igori, ariko ukaba wari umupira utari ufise inguvu nyinshi zo gutera ubwoba umunyegori wa Maroc, Yassine Bounou, azwi cane nka Bono
 Mu gihe Ronaldo yagumye yerekana ishaka, arindiriye ko aronka umupira mwiza kugira ngo akure mu kabaregwa igihugu ciwe, ntiwigeze ushika
 Igihe umupira wari utewe na Rafael Leao ku munota wa 97 ukamuca hejuru imbere y’uguterwa n’umutwe na Pepe akawutera inyuma, Ronaldo, ari muri ka gace ka mukorumbone, yakubise amavi hasi n’umwiheburo, yiremeka amaboko, icerekana ko yasa n’uwari abonye ko ivyiwe birangiye
 Ifirimbi ya nyuma imaze kuvuga, yararamukanije na bamwe mu bakeba biwe, hanyuma aca ava mu kibuga ubudakebuka, aherekejwe n’uwufata amashusho (cameraman)
 Mu kanya isase, umufana yagerageje guca mu ryahumye abajejwe umutekano arondera ingene yomusaba kwifotoza i selfie nawe, ariko biranka
 Ronaldo amaze kuzimangana mu kibuga yerekanywe ariko atera aja mu cumba c’iyambariro n’amarira, amosozi azokwibutsa ingene avuye mw’ihiganwa, hampande y’ugucanamwo n’umumenyereza wiwe
 Inyuma y’aho, Santos yafashe nk’ibisanzwe uku gucanamwo kwiwe na Ronaldo, mu kuvuga ati: "Si nibaza ko ivyashikiye Ronaldo hari ingaruka vyagize ku rukino, n’aho hari ababineguye
 Twese turi hamwe
 "Nimba twovuga ko hari abantu babiri bababaye cane, ni Ronaldo na jewe nyene
 Iki kiri mu bigize akazi ku mumenyereza n’umukinyi”
 Bafise kuba bunze ubumwe, ariko Portugal iratashe – inyuma y’ibibazo vyinshi, aho abantu bibaza nimba koko umurwi w’iki gihugu hari ico woshikako utari kumwe n’iyi nyenyeri yawo
 Ibihe biha ibindi kandi ni ibisanzwe ko imirwi ikomeye itsindwa mu nkino zikomeye, ariko, n’aho Santos yogenda canke akaguma ari umumenyereza, Ronaldo si umuntu agiye kwibagirwa vuba
 Aracafise iteka mu gihugu ciwe inyuma y’ivyo yagikoreye mu gutsindira igikombe ca Bulaya mu 2016 (Euro 2016), igikombe ca mbere gikomeye mu nkino nkuru nkuru
 Igitigiri c’abafana ba Portugal bari bambaye imipira yanditseko 'Ronaldo 7' hanze y’ikibuga Al Thumama Stadium ejo ku wa gatandatu kirerekana neza ko batibagira ibihe vyiza vya kahise kiwe n’aho ibiherutse kuba mu ndwi nkeya ziheze atari vyiza
 Mushiki wa Ronaldo, Katia Aveiro, yaravugiye abatari bake abicishije mu butumwa bwuzuye umubabaro ku rubuga rwa Instagram inyuma yo gutsindwa na Maroc
 Yatanguye ati: "Igihe abuzukuru banje bazombaza ivyerekeye urugamba, iteka, icubahiro, akazi, ukwitanga, inzitizi, ububi bw’abantu buciye kw’ishari; ni bansaba kuvuga ivyerekeye ibikombe, ibitsindo, ubushimwe, inyandiko z’umurage utarigera uboneka, nzobabwira ivyerekeye musazanje, se wabo”
 Arangiza avuga ati: "Nzobabwira ivyerekeye ubwami yubatse, nzobabwira inguvu ziwe, ivyo yemeye n’ivyo yakoze, nzobabwira amateka yiwe, nzobabwira ko atigeze acika intege n’igihe baba bamaze kumwimbira icobo
 Nzobereka firime [film], firime nyayo y’ubuzima bwa se wabo”
 Ntituzi ingene iyo firime izorangira, ariko mu gihe vyoshika agakina ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose rigira gatandatu, vyoba ari ibintu bitangaje cane
 Ico gihe, ni ukuvuga mw’ihiganwa rindi ry’igikombe c’isi yose, azoba afise imyaka 41, ariko nimba yipfuza irindi teka, aracafise amahirwe mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe ca Bulaya kizoba mu 2024
 Ikindi kibazo nyamukuru ni ukumenya ni uyuhe murwi asobora kuzoba akinira
 Hari imirwi itari mike yipfuza kugura Ronaldo muri ka kanya k’igura n’igurishwa ry’abakinyi ko mu kwa mbere, harimwo Al-Nassr  wo muri Arabia Saoudite wamaze no kumwemerera agashahara gafadika mu ndwi iheze
