Si mu Burundi gusa imisambi igeramiwe no guhona
  Kw’isi yose bigereranywa ko hasigaye iyitarenga ibihumbi 20
 Muri Uganda aho  umusambi ari ikimenyetso  c’igihugu usanga  kw’ibendera ry’igihugu, naho hari impungenge ko imisambi iriko iragabanuka cane
 Ariko ho hari imigambi yo kuyikingira
  No mu Rwanda niko bimeze
 Mu Burundi ho abadukurikira kuri Facebook benshi bavuze ko ata musambi barigera babona canke ngo bumve uvuga
 Abayizi kera nabo aho yahora ubu ntayo bakihabona
 Ariko umwigisha akaba n’umushakashatsi mu binyabuzima, Laurent Ntahuga, avuga ko 2004 mu   Burundi haharurwa imisambi irenga ijana
 Mu myaka cumi ikurikira - mu 2015 igihe yakora icigwa co kuraba iyisigaye mu Burundi -uwo mwigisha yasanze mu gihugu cose hari hasigaye ine gusa, adashizemwo iyiri mu mahoteri canke mu ngo z’abantu, nayo mike cane
 Umva aho hejuru insiguro za Laurent Ntahuga z’igituma imisambi yahonye mu Burundi n’icokorwa ngo isubire kugwira

Ntivyategerezwa kurangira uko vyarangiye
 Brezili yarakinye, iragenda gushika mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma (1/4) muri rino higanwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose, ariko rero indoto z’uko yari igiye kwerekana ubuhinga budasanzwe gushika muri finale zaraye zirangiye mu marira mu kibuga Education City Stadium
 Croatia yarakweze Brezili buke buke gushika muri wa mwanya w’ama-penalties kugira ngo iyizimirize ibizigizigi vyayo vy’igikombe kigira gatandatu, igihugu co ku mugabane wa Bulaya kikaba caraye gisubiye kuyitembagaza mu kuyikura mw’ihiganwa
 Igihe Neymar yinjiza igitsindo muri wa mwanya w’inyogera, igitsindo catumye anganya ibitsindo na ca gihangange Pele mu murwi nserukiragihugu ku ruhande rw’abagabo, vyaboneka ko yagomba abe intwari ariko yagiye kuva mu kibuga arira, muri uru rukino rushobora kuba ari rwo rwa nyuma kuri we mu gikombe c’isi yose
 Inyuma y’urukino, vyaremejwe ko umumenyereza Tite agiye gutanga imihoho, uyu mugabo w’imyaka 61 akaba yarananiwe no guha igihugu irindi teka ryokwiyongereye ku ryo yagiteye mu 2019 mu gutsindira Copa Amerika, ihiganwa ry’igikombe ca Amerika y’Epfo, mu gihe Neymar nawe yavuze ko ashobora gukukuruka mu nkino mpuzamakungu
 Bamaze gutsindwa, Tite  yavuze ati: "Mu vy’ukuri biragoye cane
 Ariko ni iherezo ryanje mu murwi nserukiragihugu wa Brezili
 Narabivuze haraciye umwaka n’inusu”
 Umuhinga mu bijanye n’umupira w’amaguru muri Amerika y’Epfo Tim Vickery yavugiye kw’iradiyo BBC Radio 5 Live ati: "Uru ni urupfu mu muryango
 "Niko bigiye kugendera abafana ba Brezili mu masaha ari imbere
 Croatia irashize mu kigandaro iki gihangange mu mupira w’amaguru
 Ni ukuri iki kizotera umubabaro w’igihe kirekire 
 "Ndizeye ko abantu batazobatako ishavu
 Abanyabrezili barashobora kurakara
 Ariko ndizeye ko ata ngaruka mbi iza kuba kuko si yo mpembo uyu murwi ukwiriye”
 Iminota 90 ya mbere yari iryoheye ijisho, ariko impande zompi vyaranse ko zitsindana, biba ngombwa ko baja muri wa mwanya w’inyongera (prolongation/Extra time)
 Croatia imaze gushika aho incuro umunani mu nkino icenda yakinye muri ca gice co gukuranamwo mu nkino nkuru nkuru
 Neymar yibajije ko yari agarukiye igihugu ciwe mu gihe nyaco cari kimukeneye cane, maze yinjiza igitsindo ku mupira bari bagiye bahererekanya n’ubuhinga bwinshi
 Igitsindo yinjije ku munota wa 106 cagize 77 atsindiye igihugu ciwe, gutyo aba anganije n’igihangange Pele nk’uko ibiharuro vya FIFA bivyerekana
 Ariko Bruno Petkovic yarakigomboye inyuma y’iminota ine gusa – mbere ukaba ari wo mupira wonyene Croatia yateye mw’igori (ikizwi nka tir cadre/shot on target) – cayigaruriye amahirwe yo kubandanya, iritwara neza ishobora gushika muri wa mwanya w’ama-penalties
 Abakeba ni bo batamvye baratarika mu gihe Neymar wewe vyanse ko yigumya mu kibuga, ararira, arihanagura, biranka! Ni we yari gutera iya gatanu ariko ntivyakunze inyuma y’aho Marquinhos atereye iya kane ikagwa ku nkingi y’igori, biba birarangiye
 Si ryo herezo rya mbere riteye agahinda kuri we
 Mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose ryabereye mu gihugu ciwe mu 2014, Neymar yarirangije n’imvune mu mugongo, ubu hakaba haciye imyaka ine bakubiswe n’Ububirigi bageze aho nyene
 Mu rukino rwa nijoro, yabaye umwe mu bakinyi bavuye mu kibuga ubwa nyuma, abafana ba Brezili bicaye mu kibuga badatahura ivyari bihejeje kuba, ivyizigiro bari bafise muri Qatar bigeye akagirire
 Tite ati: "Neymar yari kuba uwa gatanu kuko iyi niyo ikomeye
 "Umutima ntuba uri hamwe na gato, gusa abakinyi baba biteguye iyo bazi ko ari bo batera penalty ya nyuma”
 Ariko uwahoze ari umusatirizi w’Ubudagi Jurgen Klinsmann ntavyemera, aho ku mboneshakure BBC One ati: "Iyaba jewe ni we yari gutera penalty ya mbere
 Ni co gihe uba umukeneye kugira ngo ahumurize imitima”
 Urugendo rwa Brezili mu gikombe c’isi yose rwaraye rusubiriye guhagarikwa n’igihugu c’Ubulaya ku ncuro ya gatandatu yikurikiranya, igihe ca nyuma iheruka gutsinda igihugu co kuri uno mugabane hakaba hari mu 2002 itsinze Ubudagi muri finale
