 Mu kwa gatandatu 2020, haradutse igihuha cavuga ngo yapfuye, ariko ntivyari vyo, yari arajwe mu bitaro kubera indwara y’imitsi ifatira mu bwonko
 Élisabeth Tshala Muana Muidikay (yavutse ku wa 13 Rusama [5] 1958), asanzwe azwi kw’izina rya Tshala Muana yari umunyamuziki azwi cane muri Repubulika y’intwaro Rusangi ya Congo, yandika indirimbo akongera agatamba
 Afatwa nk’ “Umwamikazi wa Mutuashi", umudiho w’umuziki n’intambo vyo mu ntara ya Kasai asanzwe avukamwo, iri hagati mu gihugu
 Akunzwe kwitwa "Mamu National”, ni ukuvuga nyina w’igihugu
 Azwi cane ku ndirimbo zitari nke nka "Karibu Yangu", « Malu », «  Tshianza », « Tshibola »  n’izindi nyinshi
 Yarazungurutse mu bihugu bitari bike, atsindira ubushimwe butari buke haba mu gihugu, ku rwego rw’umugabane canke ku rwego mpuzamakungu, akaba yashoboye gusohora inkurikirane (albums) zirenga 20
