 Mu 2014, Celine Dion, ari nawe yatahanye agashimwe ka Oscar ku ndirimbo ‘My Heart Will Go On’ yabaye inziza gusumba izindi, yavuze ko agiye kuba arahagaritse umwuga wiwe wo kuririmba mu gihe atamenyesheje iherezo, kugirango yiteho umugabo wiwe Rene Angelil yari afise ingwara ya Cancer N’ubwo yasubiye muri ivyo biteramwo inyuma y’umwaka, yasubiye guhagarika uwo mwuga wiwe wo kuririmba mu 2016, inyuma y’urupfu rwa Angelil hamwe na musazawe Daniel Dion
 Yasubiye kuboneka muri studio mu 2019, igihe yakorana na Sia, Sam Smith na David Guetta album bise ‘Courage’
 Uyu mu ‘star’ yayishigikije ibiteramo hirya no hino kw’isi igihe yasohoka, vyinshi muri vyo bikaba vyarasivye kubera ikiza ca Covid-19
 Vyabaye ngombwa n’uyu mwaka nyene, kwimurira ku yandi masango ivyo biteramo, inyuma yo guhura n’iyo ngwara itera imitsi yiwe kwinyiganyiza, yanatumye adasubira ku gihe muri Las Vegas aho asanzwe aba
 Kuri uyu wa kane, Dion yaremesheje abafana biwe ababwira ko afise ‘umugwi mwiza w’abaganga bariko barakorana' kugirango bamufashe gutora mitende, mu gihe  n’abana biwe bariko baramufasha bamutera intege’
 Uyu muririnvyikazi avuga ko atari bwumve ko hageze kuvuga ivy’iyi ngwara yiwe kugeza ubu
 Yagize ati: “ndiko ndakorana n’umugwi w’abanonotsi uriko uranfasha kugirango ndabe ko noshobora gusubira kuronka utuguvu two kuriririmba, ariko ndababwiye ko bitari vyoroshe”
 Avuga ko ikintu conyene azi mu buzima ari ukuririrmba, ko ata wundi murimo yigeze akora kandi ko arivyo akunda gusumba ikintu ico arico cose
 Ati: “Ndabakumbuye cane, ndakumbuye kubabona mwese no kubateramisha
” Yongeye ko yama yitanga 100% igihe aba aremesha igiteramo ariko ngo iki gihe ivyo ntashobora kubikora muri kino gihe kubera ingwara yiwe
 Ntiyabaye agishobora kumira amosozi igihe yasezera abafana, abashimira ku buryo bamufata mu mugongo, ababwira ko igisigaye ubu ari ukwitaho ubuzima bwiwe, kandi yizeye ko ‘azotera yoroherwa’
 SPS ni ingwara idakunze kuboneka, kandi benshi badatahura
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’ikigo the National Institute for Neurological Disorders, irangwa n’imitsi yidadarika canke ikijugumiza mu buryo umugwayi adashobora kugenzura, haba mu gice c’umutumba canke mu ngingo z’amaguru n’amaboko
 Mu bindi bimenyetso umugwayi agira harimwo kutihanganira urwamo, gukorwako, canke ikindi gishobora kuvyura amarangamutima y’umugwayi, ibi vyose bigashobora gutuma imitsi yiwe itangura kunyiganyiga bitavuye ku bushake bwiwe
 Iyi ngwara irangwa n’uko umugwayi ahagarara canke yicara adatumbereye mu buryo busanzwe, nk’akarorero atunye igongo, canke imitsi yiwe ikaguma akamera nk’uwatetagaye
 Abantu bafise iyo ngwara ya SPS, bashobora kunanirwa gutambuka canke kwiyunguruza ukundi, canke bagatinya kuva mu nzu ngo baje mw’ibarabara ahari urwamo, nk’amahoni y’imidokari, bishobora gutuma umuntu aca afatwa no kunyeganyega agatemba
 Abenshi mu bafise SPS bakunda kugwa hasi, kandi kubera badafse ubushobozi bwo kwiramira, barashobora gukomereka cane
 N’ubwo SPS ata muti ifise, hariho ibifasha umurwayi - harimwo imiti ipfupfahaza ikibazo co kugabanya umwitwarariko, abantu bakagira imitsi yorohewe – bigatuma iyo ngwara idatera ikara

Na Naomi Grimley Umunyamakuru mu gisata c'amagara Ukurengerwa n'ubushuhe  birashobora kugira ingaruka ku mwana ari mu nda y'umugore mu gihe aba ariko arakorera ahantu hashushe vy'ikirenga, nk'uko vyerekanwa n'icigwa gishasha
 Ingaruka zirimwo gutuma umutima w'umwana utera cane nayo amaraso aca mu ruzogi akagabanuka
 Abashakashatsi bavuga ko hazokenerwa igikorwa kibereye kugira hakingirwe abagore  bafise inda mu gihe  ihindagurika ry'ibihe ririko rirongereza ubushuhe kw'isi yose
 Ico cigwa, cakozwe n'ishure kaminuza rya  London School of Hygiene and Tropical Medicine (LSHTM), cakurikiranye abarimyi 92 muri Gambia
 Ico cigwa casohotse mu kinyamakuru c'ubuganga n'amagara  The Lancet Planetary Health, cerekana ko kuri buri degre Celsius yongeye ku bushuhe bwari buhasanzwe, umunaniro ku mwana ari mu nda  wiyongera ku rugero rwa 17%
 N'ubwo ibindi vyigwa vyari bimaze kuraba ingaruka z'ubushuhe ku bagore bafise inda ariko bikorewe muri laboratoire mu bihugu biteye imbere, iki vyibazwa ko arico cigwa ca mbere cize ingaruka ku bantu bari mu buzima bwa minsi yose mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'iterambere
 Abo bagore bafise inda bariko barakora mu mirima y'umuceri ya West Kiang muri Gambia
 Bakora mu mirima ku zuba mu kiringo c'amasaha ari hagati y'abiri na munani
 Ubushuhe bwinshi bwabonetse muri ico gihe icigwa cariko kirakorwa bwabaye degre Celsius 45 ariko igihe c'imvura hari aho catuma bitumvikana ko hashushe gusumba
 Abo bagore basuzumwa hakoreshejwe akuma ngendanwa gafata ibipimo vy'umutima w'abana bari bibungenze
 Ibipimo vyafatwa bagira batangure gukora, umunsi w'akazi ugeze hagati hanyuma uheze
 Abo bagore bafise inda nabo nyene barakurikiranywe ku bimenyetso vyabo vy'ingene  bananizwa n'ubushuhe  nko kumeneka umutwe, kugira intege nke no kugira iseseme
 Muganga Ana Bonell,  yari arongoye ico cigwa muri  LSHTM, avuga ko ivyemeza vy'uko umwana ari mu nda yagizweko ingaruka vyatowe ku rugero rwa 33% rw'imgendo bagize muri iyo mirima
 Yavuze ati: "Twaratangaye cane tubonye ko abana bari mu nda bagirwako ingaruka n'uko ba nyina biriwe ku zuba
" "Ku mwana ari mu nda twarabonye ko  umurindi wo gutera kw'umutima waduga cane ku rugero  rubangamye hamwe twoba turi kwa muganga
 Twarabonye kandi ko hari ingaruka kw'itembera ry'amaraso kuko ingovyi nayo yagirwako ingaruka n'ubushuhe
" Avuga ko bitaba aho habereye icigwa gusa kubera ihindagurika ry'ibihe
 "Ivyo birahambaye cane ku bijanye n'uko abagore kw'isi yose bashobora gutwara inda ata ngorane bahuye
 Hagiye kubandanya hashuha gusumba kandi turazi ko iyo abagore bahuye n'ubushuhe bwinshi, ivyo bifise ingaruka zikomeye cane ku kwibaruka haba mu kuvyara  abatageze canke kuvyara abapfuye (kuruhira ubusa)
 "Twizeye ko ico cigwa kizotuma  hatahurwa neza gusumba  bimwe mu biba kugira bigende uko twabibonye, hanyuma hagire igikozwe mu kugabanya izo ngaruka ziva ku bushuhe bw'ikirenga
 " Muganga Bonell avuga ko hakenewe gukorwa ibindi vyigwa kugira hihwezwe ingene ubushuhe bw'ikirenga bugira ingaruka mu gutesha inzira amaraso aja ku mwana ari mu nda, co kimwe n'ingene ugushuhirwa kwa nyina bishobora kugira ingaruka ku buryo umwana ari mu nda atera imbere

Amerika n’Uburusiya vyakabukanije icamamare muri basketball Brittney Griner na rurangiranwa mu kudandaza ibirwanisho, Umurusiya Victor Bout, yari amaze imyaka 12 apfungiwe mw’ibohero muri Amerika
 Prezida Biden yavuze ko Griner ameze neza kandi ko ari mu ndege imukuye muri Emirats Arabes Unis (EAU)
 Avugira mu biro vyiwe White House yagize ati “Mpimbawe no kuvuga ko Brittney ameze neza… aracakeneye akanya n’ubwisanzure kugira asubize ubwenge ku murongo”
 Griner yafatiwe ku kibuga c’indege i Moscow muri Ruhuhuma (2) ahowe kuba yari afise amavuta akozwe muri cannabis (urumogi), mu kwezi guheze aca arungikwa mu kibanza bahanirwamwo
 Ubutegetsi bwa Biden bwasavye ko hoba guhanahana impfungwa mu kwezi kwa Mukakaro (7), buzi yuko Moscow yamye ishaka irekurwa rya Bout
 Ibiro ntaramakuru vyo mu Busuriya bivuga yuko yariko ararungikwa ku kibuga c’indege ca Vnukovo hafi ya Moscow
 Aho yavugira mu cumba ca White House kizwi nka Oval Office, umugore wa Griner, (Griner asanzwe yubakanye n’uwo basangiye igitsina) Cherelle, yashimagije utwigoro tw’ubutegetsi bwa Biden mu kumurekuza agira ati: “Mpagaze ngaha narengewe n’ibishobisho”
 Yongeyeko yuko ibihe yari arimwo ari bimwe muri bibi amaze gucamwo mu buzima bwiwe
 Urwandiko rwasohorewe hamwe na Arabie Saudite hamwe na EAU rwatangaje yuko nyene-inganji wa Saudi, Umuganwa Mohammed bin Salman, yafashe iyambere mu gukora ubuhuza ari kumwe na Prezida wa EAU, Mohammed bin Zayed al-Nahyan
 Uyu samuragwa w’ingoma ya Saudi afitaniye imigenderanire myiza na Prezida w’Uburusiya Vladimir Putin, kandi muri Nyakanga (9) yarafashije gutunganya uguhanahana impfungwa kutari kworoshe aho harekurwa amajana y’impfungwa zari zifiswe n’Uburusiya na Ukraine
 Igihe hatangura ibiganiro vyo kurekuza Griner mu ci riheruka, Amerika yarashimangiye yuko uwahoze ari umusirikare w’umumarine, Paul Whelan, nawe yoshirwa muri ukwo gukabukanya
 Ariko vyaciye vyigaragaza yuko Whelan, yapfunzwe mu 2018 yagirizwa gusuma urusaku, atari kwemererwa kujamwo, bica intege umuryango wiwe
 Impera n’imperuka Prezida Biden yashize umukono kw’itegeko ryo kurekura Bout, ahanagura igihano c’imyaka 25 yari yarakatiwe, akabukanywa na Griner
