 Ubuzima bwiwe bwo mw’ibanga bwaherahejwe n’igikorwa categuwe neza cane na Amerika mu 2008, aho yafatirwa kw’ihoteli yo ku murwa mukuru wa Thailand, Bangkok, bibabaza cane leta y’Uburusiya
 Haciye imyaka ibiri yararungitswe muri Amerika, akaba yari amaze imyaka 12 iheze ari mw’ibohero ryo muri Amerika yagirizwa ugufashanya n’abakora iterabwoba mu kwica Abanya-Amerika
 Nta budasa bwoboneka busumvya uburi hagati ya Bout n’uwo bakabukanijwe
