 Inyuma y’ihiganwa ryo mu matsinda ryabereyemwo ibitangaza, ubu turi mu nzira y’igikorwa nyaco, igice ca kane gishira ica nyuma kikaba cuzuye abakinyi b’ibihangange
 Itandatu mu mirwi isigaye ni iyigeze gutsindira iri higanwa canke yashitse muri finale – kandi hagati yayo imaze gutsindira iki gikombe incuro cumi
 Ariko gusa ibitangaza vyovyo bishobora gushika, aho Maroc ubu irondera kuba igihugu ca mbere ca Afrika coba gishitse mu gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma, inyuma yo gushika mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma ku ncuro ya mbere muri kahise k’umupira w’amaguru muri ico gihugu
 BBC Sport, igisata ca BBC gikurikirana inkino, irihweza bimwe mu vyitezwe, mu gihe abakinyi barondera kwerekana ubuhinga bwabo muri uru rubuga rw’umupira w’amaguru
