 Lionel Messi na Cristiano Ronaldo ni amazina agaruka cane mu binyamakuru, ariko ibihangange nka Neymar, Harry Kane, Kylian Mbappe na Luka Modric baracahagaze
 Ubwongereza n’Uburafansa – igihugu gisanzwe gifise iki gikombe – bigiye guhurira mw’ihiganwa rikomeye ku ncuro ya mbere mu myaka cumi, ikaba ari n’incuro ya mbere mu gice co gukuranamwo
 Iyi mirwi yaheruka guhura muri Euro 2012 mu nkino zo gukuranamwo aho yanganije 1-1, ariko ubwa nyuma iheruka guhura mu gikombe c’isi yose hakaba hari mu 1982
