 Kizigenza w’Ubwongereza, Kane, ati: "Ku wa gatandatu ntibizoba vyoroshe
 Ubufaransa ni umurwi ukomeye, ari na wo ufise igikombe, rero turazi ko uzoba ari umugoroba utoroshe na gato
 "Nibaza ko nimba ushaka gutsindira igikombe c’isi yose, utegerezwa guhura n’imirwi y’ibihangange kw’isi, Ubufaransa rero buri imbere”
 Ku wa Mungu, igenekerezo rya 18 Kigarama
 Urugamba rutoroshe ku kibuga ca Lusail i Doha
 Ibihangange bibiri kw’isi mu gihe cabo bararwanira ubugabo, akaryo kabo ka nyuma  ko kurwanira iri teka ry’igikombe c’isi yose
 Ubutigu bwageze
 Messi wa Argentina hamwe na Ronaldo wa Portugal bamaze imyaka baterana inkokora umwe wese arondera kwandika amateka
 Muri rino higanwa ryonyene, Messi yinjije igitsindo ku rukino rwiwe rwari rugize 1000 igihe bahura na Australia mu gice c’umunani gishira ica nyuma, mu gihe Ronaldo nawe yabaye umukinyi wa mbere yinjije ibitsindo mu mahinganwa atanu yose y’igikombe c’isi yose
 Bompi baramaze gutsindira igikombe c’amahiganwa ku migabane yabo – Messi yatsindiye Copa America mu mwaka uheze, mu gihe Ronaldo yari yatsindiye ihiganwa rya Bulaya mu 2016 – ariko iki gikombe ca mbere nyamukuru kw’isi kiracari umugani kuri bo
 Ku myaka 35 Messi aboneka ko ari ryo higanwa rya nyuma ry’igikombe c’isi yose kuri we, mu gihe Ronaldo wewe azoba afise imyaka 41 mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose kizokurikira
 Aha ata nkeka biraboneka ko ari yo mahirwe ya nyuma kuri bo yo gushobora guterura iki gikombe c’iteka
 Hagati aho, vyabaye ngombwa ko Ronaldo yemera ko yari afise uruhara ruto mu rukino rwa Portugal rw’igice c’umunani gishira ica nyuma - aho yashizwe ku rutonde rw’abagombora, mu gihe uwamutwaye ikibanza Goncalo Ramos w’imyaka 21 yakoze ibintu bidasanzwe mu gutera bitatu wenyene mu rukino rwabo n’Ubuswisi
 Nko mu gihe vyoshika ibi bihangange bigahurira muri finale, ivy’ari vyo vyose n’abatagira aho begamire bogira amero
 None twizere ko impari kuri ‘GOAT’ (impfunyapfunyo ya Greatest Of All Time, twogereranya na ‘Igihangange c’ibihe vyose) zishobora kuba zigiye guhera? Imbere y’aho, birashoboka ko turorera urukino ruryoheye ijisho rwo mu gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma
 Mu gihe yompi yorengana Croatia n’Ubuholande uko ikurikirana, urugamba rw’agakura muri Amerika y’Ubumanuko ni rwo rwokurikira hagati ya Brezili na Argentina ku kibuga ca Lusail
 Brezili, igihugu kimaze gutahukana iri higanwa incuro zitanu kandi kikaba ari co gihabwa amahirwe menshi, yarerekanye ubuhinga bwayo mu kwirahira bikomeye Korea y’Epfo, mu gihe Argentina yari ikeneye ubuhinga bwa kizigenza wayo Messi kugira ngo ishire Australia ku ruhande
 Iyi mirwi imaze guhura incuro zine mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose, ariko ubwa nyuma iheruka guhura hakaba hari mu 1990, igihe igitsindo ca Claudio Caniggia mu minota ya nyuma y’urukino cahaye akaryo Argentina ko kwinjira mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma
 Amahirwe yo kuvana iki gikombe i Bulaya ari cane cane mu minwe y’ino mirwi ibiri, Brezili ikaba ari co gihugu ca nyuma kitari ico ku mugabane wa Bulaya giheruka gutsindira iki gikombe, hari mu 2002
 Igihangange Neymar yarakize imvune yo mw’ivi yari yanduye mu rukino rwabo rwa mbere, yongera araninjiza igitsindo mu gice c’umunani gishira ica nyuma na Korea y’Epfo, ubu akaba akeneye igitsindo kimwe gusa kugira ngo anganye n’igihangange Pele ku bitsindo 77 mu murwi nserukiragihugu wa Brezili, uzwi nka Selecao
 Ariko Croatia ya Luka Modric hamwe n’Ubuholande bwa Virgil van Dijk navyo bifise ijambo rikomeye mu kwemeza nimba iki kirori kizoshoboka canke kitazoshoboka
 Tugiye ku Buholande, uyu murwi wa Louis van Gaal hamwe na Argentina ni abakeba bamenyeranye cane muri rino higanwa, biteze guhura ku ncuro ya gatandatu barwanira itike yo mu gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma
 Ni isubiramwo rya finale yo mu 1978, aho uyu murwi wo muri Amerika y’Ubumanuko ari wo watahukanye intsinzi, mu gihe urukino rwa nyuma iyi mirwi yaheruka guhuriramwo ari urwabaye mu myaka umunani iheze, Argentina ikaba ari yo yatsinze ku ma penalties
 Ariko kimwe mu bihe ntibagiranwa - atari gusa hagati y’ibi bihugu ariko muri kahise k’igikombe c’isi yose – ni icabaye mu 1998 igihe Dennis Bergkamp yinjiza igitsindo ciza cane cahaye akaryo Ubuholande kubandanya mu gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma
 "Dennis Bergkamp, Dennis Bergkamp, Dennis Bergkamp," niko umunyamakuru w’Ubuholande yiha karuru avuga igihe uyu mukinyi yakinira Arsenal yakubita icenga n’ubuhinga bwinshi ku mupira yari ahawe na Frank de Boer, aca aroba Roberto Ayala maze yinjiza igitsindo ciza cane
