 Itsinzi yabo yatumye bashika mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yashimagijwe n’ubwami bw’ico gihugu, aho umumenyereza Walid Regragui yahamagawe kuri terefone n’umwami  wa Maroc Mohammed VI urukino ruheze
 Umurwi upanze neza kandi ugoye gutsinda, Maroc ni urutare,  ntirigera itsindwa na rimwe muri rino higanwa ry’iki gikombe c’isi yose, ikaba imaze kwinjizwa igitsindo kimwe gusa mu nkino zabo indwi ziheruka
 Maroc kibaye igihugu ca kane c’umugabane wa Afrika gishitse mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma, kikaba kiriko kirondera itike yo gushika mu gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma
 Hagati aho, ni ikindi gipimo gikomeye kiyirindiriye imbere y’uyu murwi w’i Bulaya – na rirya Portugal nayo iriko irondera kwandikisha amateka mu kurondera gushika mu gice ca nyuma ku ncuro ya mbere

Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine yagendeye ingabo zirwanira mu ntara ya Donetsk, intara Uburusiya buvuga ko ari iyabwo inyuma ya kamarampaka y’amanyanga
 Aka karere – cane cane mu micungararo y’igisagara ca Bakhmut – niko ubu kaberamwo intambara zikomeye inyuma y’uko ingabo za Ukraine zisubije Kherson mu bumanuko mu kwezi guheze
 Uburusiya n’abakorana nabwo bagenzura uduce twa Donetsk kuva mu 2014
 Ku mugoroba w’ejo ku wa kabiri, hari ibindi bitero bishasha vy’amabombe vyavuzwe mu ntara ya Dnipropetrovsk iri hagati amaja mu buseruko
 Umuntu umwe yarakomeretse igihe inyubakwa y’uruganda iterwa mu gisagara ca Kryvyi Rih, nk’uko bivugwa n’umukuru w’iyo ntara Valentyn Reznichenko
 Ibi bibaye inyuma y’aho ku wa mbere Uburusiya bucucagiriye ibisasu vya misire ku bibanza vya gisivire muri Ukraine
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije ku musi wahariwe ingabo ejo ku wa kabiri, Zelensky yavuze ko intambara yo mu micungararo ya Bakhmut ari "iyo mu karere kagoye gusumba ahandi, kadakingiye  ubuseruko bwonyene, ahubwo gakingiye igihugu cose”
 Ariko avuga ko yizeye ko Ukraine izoshobora kwisubiza ubutaka bwose bwigaruriwe n’Uburusiya, harimwo Crimea – ikirwa ca Ukraine kiri mu bumanuko cihagiwe n’Uburusiya haraciye imyaka umunani
 Haheze amayinga atari make hari intambara mu micungararo ya Bakhmut mu gihe Uburusiya buriko bugerageza kwigarurira ubundi butaka inyuma y’uturere tutari duke bwatakaje ku rugamba muri Ukraine
 Igisata c’Ubwongereza kijejwe igendereza cemeza ko urugamba rw’Uburusiya muri ako karere rurongowe n’umurwi wigenga wa gisirikare, umurwi Wagner
 Bivugwa ko impande zompi zimaze gutakaza ibintu n’abantu benshi muri ako karere
 Urugamba rwa Bakhmut rugereranywa n’urugamba rwo mu ntambara ya mbere y’isi yose kubera imyobo, ibiti vyaturiwe n’ivyondo, ibiranga ino ntambara
 Perezida Zelensky arashimagiza ingabo ku butwari bwazo n’ukwihangana, muri video yafatiwe mu gisagara ca Sloviansk, ku birometero vyababa 40 mu buraruko bushira uburengero bwa Bakhmut
  Sloviansk ni kimwe mu bisagara vyari vyigaruriwe n’ingabo zari zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya mu 2014, ariko mu nyuma kikaba cahavuye cisubizwa na Ukraine
 Mu nyuma ejo ku wa kabiri, Zelensky yagendeye abasirikare ba Ukraine bakomeretse bariko baravurirwa mu bitaro mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw’intara ya Kharkiv
 Hagati aho, umukuru w’igisagara ca Donetsk kikiri mu minwe y’Uburusiya, avuga ko ibisasu vyatewe na Ukraine vyishe abantu batandatu
 Ku wa mbere, haratewe ibibombe ku bibuga vy’indege bibiri hagati mu Burusiya, Moscou ikavuga ko vyakozwe n'indege zitagira abadereva (drones) za Ukraine
 Ikindi kibombe caturikiye hafi y’ikibuga c’indege mu ntara ya Kursk ihana urubibe na Ukraine naco nyene cagirijwe Ukraine
 Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya yahavuye akoranya abategetsi bo hejuru kugira bavugane ku kibazo c’”umutekano w’igihugu”, ariko nta nsiguro zatanzwe

Na  Harry Poole Umunyamakuru w'inkino wa BBC Imbere y’uko urukino rutangura, havugwa gusa ivyo kudakinisha Cristiano Ronaldo
 Ariko ifirimbi ya nyuma iheze, ivyavugwa vyose vyari kuri Goncalo Ramos
 Igihe afata ikibanza ku ntebe y’abasubirizi mu rukino rwa nijoro n’Ubuswisi mu gice c’umunani gishira ica nyuma mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose muri Qatar, amakamera yose (cameras) yari yarabishijwe kuri uno mukinyi amaze kwinjiriza Portugal ibitsindo vyinshi gusumba abandi bakinyi bose muri kahise k’umupira muri ico gihugu
 Inyifato yagize igihe asubirizwa mu rukino rwaheruka yararakaje umumenyereza Fernando Santos
 Intebe yari ikikujwe n’abafotozi barwana barondera gufata isanamu ya Ronaldo yari ababaye kubera atari ku rutonde rw’abakinyi 11 bategerezwa gutangura mu rukino rukomeye nk’uru
 Bwari bwo bwa mbere bimugendeye uko kuva mu 2008
 Ariko rero haciye akanya gato, amaso yose yaciye ahindukirira ku vyariko bibera mu kibuga, aho umukinyi w’imyaka 21 yamusubiriye yandikishije izina mu gutsinda ibitsindo bitatu vyose muri uru rukino rwarangiye Portugal inyagiye Ubuswisi 6-1
 Igihe umumenyereza wa Portugal Santos afata ingingo yo kudatanguza Ronaldo muri uru rukino, ntiyari yiteze ibintu vyiza nk’ivyo yaraye abonye
 Uretse ko umurwi wiwe watsinze ibitsindo bitandatu mu gice co gukuranamwo mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose, umusore yakinishije mu kibanza ca Ronaldo yateye ibitsindo bitatu wenyene muri iri joro rya mbere rikomeye kuva atanguye umwuga wiwe
 Ku myaka 21 n’imisi 169, Ramos ni we mukinyi wa mbere akiri muto yinjije ibitsindo bitatu mu rukino rumwe mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose kuva ku munya-Hongrie Florian Albert mu 1962
 Uyu musatirizi wa Benfica vyamusavye iminota 17 gusa kugira atangaze izina ryiwe muri Qatar, igihe atera umupira ugaca iruhande y’umunyegori w’Ubuswisi Yann Sommer hejuru mu mfuruka z’igori, aba ashize Portugal imbere
 Inyuma y’iminota mikeya igice ca kabiri gitanguye, yateye igitsindo ciwe ca kabiri ku mupira wo hasi yari ahawe na Diogo Dalot, maze biba bibaye 3-0
 Igitsindo ca Raphael Guerreiro cinjiye imbere y’uko Ramos atera iciwe ca gatatu muri urwo rukino – ubwa mbere muri rino higanwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose – igitsindo yinjije arovye umunyegori Sommer
 Yagiye gusubirizwa ku munota wa 74 amaze gutera ibitsindo vyiwe bitatu, tutavuze imipira yahereje n’iyo yateye mw’igori ishika itanu
 Igihe Ramos yari asubirijwe, Rob Green yahoze ari umunyegori w’Ubwongereza yavugiye kuri BBC Radio 5 Live ati: " Goncalo Ramos yakoze ibintu bitangaje
 Ivya mbere muri kino gikombe c’isi yose gushika ubu, n’ibindi vyose vyoba bimaze kuba”
 Mu gihe Ronaldo atarashobora kwinjiza igitsindo na kimwe mu nkino zitandatu zose zo gukuranamwo Portugal imaze gukina muri rino higanwa, n’aho amaze kwinjiza ibitsindo umunani mu mahiganwa y’igikobe c’isi yose, Ramos wewe amaze kwinjiza bitatu
 Ramos, umukinyi yakuriye mu murwi w’urwaruka rwa Benfica, yari amaze gukinira Portugal iminota 33 yonyene mu nkino zitatu yari amaze gukina, imbere y’uko igihugu ciwe gihura n’Ubuswisi nijoro ku wa kabiri
 Aha harimwo iminota 23 yakinye mu rukino rwa kivandimwe Portugal yahuye na Nigeria mu kwa cumi na rimwe rwarangiye Portugal itsinze Nigeria igitsindo kimwe ku busa, iminota ibiri mu rukino rwa Ghana hamwe n’iyindi umunani yakinye mu rwa Uruguay mu nkino zo mu matsinda
 Kuva ico gihe yashizwe ku rutonde rw’abasubirizi akaba atakinishijwe igihe Portugal itsindwa na Korea ya Ruguru, ariko ikaba yari yamaze kuronka itike yo kubandanya
 Hagati aho, inyuma yo gushirwa ku rutonde rw’abatangura mu kibuga ku ncuro ya mbere ku rwego mpuzamakungu  mu nkino zo gukuranamwo muri rino higanwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose, yakoze ibintu bikomeye aboneka nk’uko umengo ni ibintu yari amaze imyaka myinshi akora
 Ku bitsindo 14 n’imipira itandatu yatanze ikavamwo ibitsindo mu nkino 21 za Benfica muri uno mwaka w’inkino – hiyongereyeko ibitsindo indwi yinjije mu nkino zitandatu mw’ihiganwa riheruka – Ramos nta nkeka ubu ni umukinyi yiyemera
 Ariko indoto yonyene yari afise ni ukungene yari kuvyifatamwo ku rukino rwiwe rwa mbere ashizwe ku rutonde rw’abatangura mu kibuga mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose
 Ni we mukinyi wa mbere yinjije ibitsindo bitatu, ikizwi nka hat-trick, ku rukino rwiwe rwa mbere atangujwe mu kibuga mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi kuva ku mudagi Miroslav Klose mu 2002- umukinyi wa mbere amaze kwinjiza ibitsindo vyinshi mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi ku ruhande rw’abagabo – akaba kandi n’umukinyi akiri muto agira kabiri amaze kwinjiriza Portugal ibitsindo muri kahise k’ik igihugu mu gikombe c’isi yose, inyuma ya Ronaldo mu 2006
 Inyuma y’urukino rudasanzwe rwa nijoro, arumva neza ko yakoze ivyo yashobora gukora vyose kugira ngo igihugu ciwe kibandanye mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma aho kizohura na Maroc
 Abajijwe ivya Ronaldo ifirimbi ya nyuma ivuze, Ramos yavuze ati: "Cristiano Ronaldo aramvugisha kandi avugisha uwo ari we wese mu murwi
 Ni we kizigenza wacu kandi yama agerageza kudufasha”
 Irangira ry’urukurikirane rw’inkino 31 atanguzwa mu kibuga  kuri uyu yahoze ari umusatirizi wa Real Madrid, Juventus na Manchester United ryategerezwa kuba inkuru ikomeye cane
 Ariko na we nyene ashobora kuba yaratangajwe n’ingene yavuzwe cane imbere y’uko urukino rwa nijoro rutangura, mu gihe ikintu kinini yashoboye gukorera abakunzi baguma basaba ko yinjizwa mu gice ca kabiri ari igitsindo canswe kubera yari yaraririye
 Uravye ivyo Ramos yaraye akoze, nta cizere kinini asigaranye c’uko ku myaka 37 Ronaldo azohava asaba gutanguzwa mu kibuga mu rukino rwo ku wa gatandatu aho Portugal izoba ihura na Maroc
 Umumenyereza wa Portugal Santos avuga  ati "koko sinashimishijwe" n’inyifato ya Ronaldo igihe asubirizwa ku munota wa 65 igihe itsindwa na Korea y’Epfo mu rukino rwa nyuma rwo mw’itsinda ryabo, bikaba bisa n’ingene yaje kurangiza giturumbuka muri Manchester United mu kwezi guheze
 Uyu mukinyi yatsindiye Ballon d’Or (Umupira w’Inzahabu) incuro zitanu arahakana ko atarakariye umumenyereza wiwe, ariko ibi nticabujije ko yisanga ku rutonde rw’abasubirizi mu rukino n’Ubuswisi
 Inyuma yo kuba umukinyi wa mbere yinjije ibitsindo mu mahiganwa atanu y’igikombe c’isi yose imbere y’aha, ibitangaza umurwi wiwe waraye ukoze bishobora gutuma Ronaldo ata kundi vyogenda atari kwemera ikibanza giciriritse mu gihugu ciwe
 Mu kiganiro n’imboneshakure ITV, uwahoze ari umusatirizi w’Ubwongereza, Ian Wright avuga ati: "Uyu ni umurwi ushobora neza na neza kubandanya gushika kw’iherezo kandi Ronaldo aracashoboye gufasha
 "Mu gihe yokwipanga neza, birashobora kurangira abinjirije igitsindo c’intsinzi mu rukino rwa nyuma”

Reta ya Afrika y'Epfo yateye akamo abantu ko bategerezwa gukurikiza akarorero k'umugabo w'umuzungu yafashwe video yakwiragiye henshi, ariko ariyamiriza amacakubiri ashingiye ku rukoba
 Iyo video imwerekana ahanganye na ba nyene akabare b'abazungu mu gisagara ca Cape Town, ababaza impamvu babujije mugenzi we w'umwirabire kukinjiramwo
 Itangazo rya reta ryasohotse ku musi wa kabiri, ririyamiriza ryivuye inyuma "iyo nyifato y'amacakubiri ashingiye ku rukoba yabaye igihe Thabiso Danca w'imyaka 25 yabuzwa kwinjira mu bunywero w'aba Irlandais, Hank's Olde, mu gisagara ca Cape Town, kubera gusa ari umwirabure, kandi akaba adaherekejwe n'umuzungu"
 Iyo video ubu imaze kurabwa n'abantu ibihumbi amajana, yatanguye gukwiragizwa ku musi wa gatanu
 Yerekana umugenzi wa Danca, Christopher Logan, aja muri ubwo bunywero guhangana n'umwe muri banyene akabare kuri ivyo vyavugwa ko ari amacakubiri ashingiye ku rukoba
 Yabwiye nyene akabare ko uwucungera umutekano yabwiye umugenzi wiwe: "Ntushobora kwinjira ngaha, atawuguherekeje, ata muzungu muri kumwe
" Nyene ubunywero yishuye ko ivyo ata kibazo vyari bwatere mu myaka 18 amaze adandaza
 Ubwo bunywero bwaciye busohora itangazo buhakana kugira inyifato y'amacakubiri ashingiye ku rukoba, bashira n'ikimenyetso hanze  cerekana ko ata macakubiri n'amwe aharangwa
 Ico kimenyetso canditseko: "Dushaka kwemeza  ko mu myaka 30 iheze dukorera urudandaza aha muri Cap Town, twebwe nka banyene aka kabare, tutarigera, canke ngo dutegeke abakozi bacu, kwinuba umuntu hitwaje ikintu ico ari co cose, haba igitsina, kamere k'uburyo umuntu ahuza igitsina n'uwundi,  canke urukoba
" Reta yasavye ko haba "amatohoza yihuta kuri ivyo vyabaye, kandi n'ubutungane bukore
" Reta "yahamagariye abanye Afrika y'epfo bose gukurikiza akarorero ka Logan no kwiyamiriza amacakubiri afatiye ku rukoba"

Na Paul Kirby BBC News Abantu 25 bafashwe mu Budagi bakekwa kuba bariko barategura gutembagaza reta
 Amakuru y’aho mu Budagi avuga ko uwo mugwi w’abantu bo muri ‘extreme droite’ kandi bigeze kuba ari abasirikare bari bateguye gutera inyubakwa y’inama nshingamateka, Reichstag, hanyuma bafate ubutegetsi
 Umuntu wo mu miryango yubahwa avugwa nka  Prince Heinrich XIII, w’imyaka  71,bivugwa ko ari we yari indongozi muri uwo mugambi
 Ku bw’abashikirizamanza  ku rwego rw’igihugu, ni umwe mu mugwi w’abantu bari imbere muri uwo mugambi bafashwe mu ntara 11 zo mu mu Budagi
 Abariko barategura uwo mugambi bivugwa ko barimwo abo mu muhari w’ivyiyumviro bikaze (extremiste)  wa Reichsbürger, wari usanzwe ushinzwe ijisho n’igiporisi c’Ubudagi kubera ibitero birimwo intureka n’insiguro zishingiye ku rukoba ku bibazo vy’igihugu
 Baranka kandi kwemera Ubudagi bwa none
 Abandi  bikekwa bavuye mu muhari QAnon w'abemera ko igihugu cabo kiri mu minwe ya reta 'y'ibitito (myths)' irimwo ubutegetsi bwo mu kinyegero buguma bukwega bujana iyo bushaka
 Umushikiranganji w'intwaro yo hagati Nancy Faeser yijeje Abadagi ko abategetsi bazokoresha inguvu zose z'amategeko "ku bansi ba demokrasi
" Bigereranywa ko abagabo n’abagore 50 boba  bari muri uwo mugwi, washaka gutembagaza intwaro ya repuburika ukayisubiriza igihugu gishasha gishingiye ku Budagi bwo mu 1871 -ubwami bwitwa Reich ya Kabiri (Second Reich)
 Umugore avugira ibiro vy’abashikirizamanza yavuze ati ”nta zina ry’uwo mugwi turamenya
” Abaporisi 3
000  nibo  bagiye muri ico gikorwa  c’imikwabu 130 yabaye henshi mu gihugu cose, hakaba hari n’abantu babiri  bafatiwe muri Australia no mu Butaliyano
  Abafashwe bagapfungwa vyitezwe ko basambishwa uyu munsi
 Umushikiranganji ajejwe ubutungane Marco Buschmann  yanditse kuri Twitter ko hariko haraba igikorwa gikomeye co kurwanya iterabwoba kandi hikekwa kuba hari hateguwe ”igitero gikomeye ku nzego zamuka kw’ibwirizwa shingiro”
 Umushikirizamanza ku rwego rw’igihugu avuga ko uwo mugwi watanguye gutegura gutembagaza ubutegetsi biciye mu ntureka kuva muri Munyonyo mu 2021 kandi ko abo muri komite yo kubitegura, Rat, kuva ico gihe bakora amanama buri igihe
 Umushikirizamanza yavuze ko bari bamaze gupanga n’ibisata vy’ubutegetsi bwabo birimwo amagara, ubutungane n’imigenderanire n’amakungu
 Abagize uwo mugwi bumva ko bari gushika ku migambi yabo bakoresheje ”uburyo bwa gisirikare n’intureka ku baserukira inzego z’igihugu” harimwo no kwica
 Abakora amatohoza bivugwa ko bamenye uwo mugwi igihe batora ko hari umugambi wo kunyuruza mu kwezi kwa Ndamukiza(4)  w'akagwi kiyita United Patriots (Inkundagihugu zunze Ubumwe)
 Nabo nyene bari mu bagize uwo mugambi wa Reichsbürger kandi ko woba wari wateguye kunyuruza umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara  Karl Lauterbach bakongera bagatuma haba ibihe nk’’ivy’intambara yo hagati mu gihugu” kugira harangire demokrasi mu Budagi
 Heinrich XIII ava mu muryango w’i bukuru wa kera uzwi nka Reuss, watwaye ibice vy’intara ya none yo mu buseruko ya  Thuringia gushika mu 1918
  Abana bose b’abahungu b’uwo muryango bahabwa izina rya  Heinrich hamwe n’igiharuro
 Uretse gutembagaza reta, ababitegura bari bafise imigambi yo gishinga ishami rya gisirikare, ririmwo abasanzwe n’abahoze mu gisirikare , nk’uko amakuru avuga
 Barimwo  abahoze mu nzego za gisirikare zidasanzwe
 Intumbero y’iryo shami rya gisirikare kwari ukuvanaho inzego za demokarasi mu butegetsi bwo hasi , nk’uko abashikirizamanza bavuga
 Umwe mu bariko barakorwako amatohoza ni uwuri mu ngabo za Special Commando , abaporisi basatse inzu  n’icumba vyiwe mw’ikambi ya gisirikare ya Graf-Zeppelin muri Calw mu bumanuko bushira uburengero bwa Stuttgart

N﻿a Paul Adams & Ben Tobias BBC News Uburusiya bwateye ibisasu vya misire ku bibanza bitari bike muri Ukraine ku ncuro igira umunani mu mayinga umunani
 Hari amakuru avuga ko ibigo vy’amasoko ntanganguvu vyononekaye cane, cane cane mu buseruko
 Mu bumanuko, igisagara ca Odesa nta muyagankuba gifise
 Ukraine ivuga ko abantu bane bishwe
 Ariko ibi bitero bije inyuma y’indwi hafi zibiri habaye ivyaheruka bishobora kuba bitononye ibintu vyinshi nk’ivyabaye imbere y’aha
 Ukraine ivuga ko yasambuye 60 muri 70 vyarashwe n’Uburusiya
 Moscou (umugwa mukuru w'Uburusiya) ivuga ko yagemye ibibanza 17 vyose yari yateguye gutera
 Mu butumwa bwiwe yacishije kuri videwo mu masaha yitereye y’ejo ku wa mbere, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine yavuze ko ivyo bitero vyatewe ku bigo vy’umuyagankuba mu gihugu kibanyi ca Moldavie/Moldova
 "Iki gisubiye kwerekana ko ubushobozi bw’Uburusiya bwo gukora ibi bitero vy’iterabwoba ari akaga, atari kuri Ukraine gusa, ariko mu karere kacu kose”
 Ibitero vy’Uburusiya biheruka vyakozwe ku bigo ntanganguvu, bituma imiriyoni z’abanyagihugu babura umuyagankuba n’uburyo bwo kwishusha mu gihe igihe c’ubukonje cashitse
 Hari haciye imisi itari mike abanyagihugu bagabishijwe ko Uburusiya bwariko butegura ikindi gihuhusi c’ibisasu vya misire
 Bigiye kuba inyuma y’amasaha make habaye ibibombe vyaturikiye ku birindiro bibiri vya gisirikare imbere hagati mu Burusiya, Mosou ikavuga ko ari igitero cakozwe na za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) za Ukraine zakorowe n’igisirikare c’Uburusiya kirwanira mu kirere
 Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Uburusiya buvuga ko abasirikare batatu ari bo bishwe indege zibiri nazo zirononekra bukebuke muri ivyo bibombe
 Ukraine ntaco irabivugako
 Ku ba enjeniyeri b'umuyagankuba ba Ukraine basanzwe batorohewe na gato, ibitero vya misire vyo ku wa mbere vyerekana ko bagiye kugira akandi kazi gashasha ko gusanura, ku bibanza vyarashwe kenshi mu ndwi ziheruka
 Imbere y’ibitero vya nijoro, abategesi ba Kyiv (umugwa mukuru wa Ukraine) bariko bavuga ukuntu bova mu bihe bidasanzwe vyo gucika kenshi kw’umuyagankuba, bakaja mu gihe co kuyaca mu buryo buteguye bigaha abasivire akoyoko mu kubaronsa umuyagankuba mu gihe kanaka baba bayakeneye cane
 Izi nteguro zishobora kubangirwako, n’aho ibitero vy’ejo ku wa mbere bishobora kuba vyagize ingaruka atari nini ugereranije n’ivy’imbere y’ha
 Ikindi kintu gitangaje cibonekeje muri bino bitero vy’Uburusiya ni ingene bisa n’uko za drones z’ubwiyahuzi za Irani zitarimwo
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine baherutse kuvuga ko Uburusiya bwaherewe n’izi ndege zitagira abadereva
 Uwundi mutegetsi wa Ukraine avuga ko Uburusiya bwananiwe no kuzirungika muri iki gihe c’ubukonje
 Uko vyagenze kwose, zisa n‘uko zitarakoreshwa kuva hagati mu kwa cumi na rimwe
 Uburusiya bwatanguye ibi bitero bikomeye ku masoko ntanganguvu ya Ukraine ku wa 10 z’ukw’icumi
 Kuva ico gihe, hafi igice c’amasoko ntanganguvu y’igihugu yarononekaye, ivyatumye amamiriyoni y’abanya-Ukraine bisanga ata muyagankuba bafise mu gihe ibipimo vy’ubushuye vyagiye musi y’ubusa kubera ubukonje
 Bamwe mu bategetsi b’Uburengero bavuga ko ibi bitero ari ivyaha vyo mu ntambara, kubera urugero rurengeje bw’ubwononyi bwakozwe ku bibanza vya gisivire
 Ibitero ku bibanza vy’umuyagankuba si ngombwa ngo vyitwe ko ari ihonyangwa ry’amategeko mpuzamakungu, ariko bitegerezwa kuba ku rugero rumwe n’inyungu za gisirikare izo ari zo zose zabonetse
 Abahinga babwiye BBC ko  amayeri y’Uburusiya yo gutera amasoko ntanganguvu ashobora kuba afise intumbero yo guca ivutu no gutera ubwoba abanyagihugu, aho kubuzanira akarusho kaboneka
 Ibi bishobora kuba ari ihonyangwa ry’amategeko mpuzamakungu, nk’uko biri mu masezerano ya Geneva

Inama nshingamateka ya Indonesia kuri uno wa kabiri yemeje itegeko mpanavyaha rishasha rizohanisha umunyororo wo gushika ku mwaka umwe abasambanyi
 Iri tegeko riri mu rukurikirane rw’impinduka abanegura reta bavuga ko zititura ubwigenge bwa poritike
 Iri tegeko mpanavyaha rishasha ntirishobora kuja mu ngiro imbere y’imyaka itatu, rikaba ririmwo kandi no guhana uwutuka umukuru w’igihugu n’uwushikiriza ivyiyumviro biteye kubiri n’amarangamutima ya reta
 Amashirahamwe mato mato yakoze imyiyerekano imbere y’inama nshingamateka ku mugwa mukuru Jakarta ejo ku wa mbere
 Iri tegeko mpanavyaha – rizofata abanya-Indonesia n’abanyamahanga – ririmwo amategeko atari make “yerekeye inyifato” kandi rirahana ababana batarubakana bagahuza ibitsina
 Umukunzi canke abavyeyi bashobora kumushengeza ku caha co gusambana
 Kurenga ibigo (guca inyuma uwo mwashakanye, mu Kinyarwanda) naco nyene kizoba icaha gishobora gutuma abantu bapfungwa
 Hagati aho, iri tegeko mpanavyaha rishasha riraja no mu bindi bisata vy’ubuzima bw’igihugu, amashirahamwe aharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu akavuga ko ari nko guhonyanga uburenganzira butangwa n’intwaro rusangi
 Ririmwo ingingo zijanye no gutuka abakuru zibuza abantu gutuka umukuru w’igihugu canke gushikiriza ivyiyumviro biteye kubiri n’amarangamutima y’igihugu
 Ririmwo kandi “ingingo ziteye ingorane” zihonyanga uburenganzira bw’abagore, abari muri wa murwi w’abahuza ibitsina babisangiye hamwe n’abo mu madini y’inkehwa, nk’uko Elaine Pearson, arongoye ishirahamwe Human Rights Watch ku mugabane wa Aziya, abivuga
 Umupfasoni Pearson yabwiye BBC ati: "Iyi ni inzitizi ikomeye cane ku gihugu kigerageza kwiyerekana ko kigengwa n’intwaro ya ki-Islam igendera kuri demokarasi”
 Umushakashatsi wo muri iryo shirahamwe ari i Jakarta, Andreas Harsono, avuga ko hari amamiriyoni n’amamiriyoni y’ababanye muri Indonesia badafise impapuro zemeza ko bubakanye “cane cane mu basangwabutaka canke aba-Islam mu mitumba ya kure” usanga barongoranye babicishije mw’idini
 Yabwiye BBC ati: "Aba bantu vyumvikana ko bazoba bariko bahonyanga itegeko kuko kubana bishobora guhanishwa umunyororo wo gushika ku mezi atandatu”
 Yongerako y’uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Kigobe c’Abarabu, ahasanzwe hari amategeko asa n’ayo yerekeye ivyo guhuza ibitsina, bwerekana ko abagore ari bo  bahanwa kandi biziziwe n’aya mategeko agenga inyifato gusumba abagabo
 Hagati aho, abashingamateka ba Indonesia bavuga ko ririmwo ingingo zikingira uburenganzira bwo gushikiriza ivyiyumviro n’imyiyerekano ikozwe ku “nyungu z’abanyagihugu”
 Bishimira kandi kubona iri tegeko ryemejwe, na rirya ritari bwigere risubirwamwo kuva Indonesia ironse intahe y’ukwikukira yibohoye ubutegetsi bw’Ubuholande
 Integuro y’iri tegeko yaheruka, yategerezwa kwemezwa mu 2019 ariko yateje imyiyerekano igihugu cose aho abantu ibihumbi mirongo bayitabiriye
 Abenshi, harimwo n’abanyeshure, barihaye amabarabara mbere haraba no gutana mu mitwe n’igipolisi muri Jakarta
 Uturere tumwe tumwe twa Indonesia twari dusanzwe dufise amategeko ruhasha ashingiye kw’idini ku vyerekeye uguhuza ibitsina
 Intara ya Aceh isanzwe yubahiriza itegeko rikomeye rya Islam, ikaba ihana abakina akamari (imikino y'amahirwe, mu Kinyarwanda), abanywa inzoga no guhura n’abantu mudasangiye igitsina

N﻿a Siavash Ardalan & Marita Moloney BBC Persian Umushikirizamanza mukuru w’igihugu avuga ko igipolisi kijejwe inyifato, ari naco kijejwe kwubahiriza itegeko rya Islam rijejwe inyambaro muri Irani, kiriko kirasenyurwa
 Amajambo ya Mohammad Jafar Montazeri, n’aho ataremezwa n’ibindi bisata, yashikirijwe mu birori vyariko biba ejo ku wa Mungu
 Irani imaze amezi atari make mu myiyerekano yaturutse ku rupfu rw’umugore yari akiri muto yapfiriye mu gasho
 Mahsa Amini yari yapfunzwe n’igipolisi kijejwe inyifato camwagiriza ko yahonyanze amabwirizwa ajanye no kwitwikira
 Montazeri yari mw’ikoraniro ry’amadini igihe abazwa niba igipolisi kijejwe inyifato kiriko kirasamburwa
 Yavuze ati: "Igipolisi kijejwe inyifato ntaco gisa gisana n’ubutungane kandi carugawe kuva aho catanguriye”
 Iki gipolisi kigenzurwa n’ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati, ntikigenzurwa n’ubutungane
 Ku wa gatandatu, Montazeri yabwiye kandi inama nshingamateka ya Irani ko ibwirizwa ritegeka abagore kwambara wa mwambaro wa hijab rigiye kwihwezwa
 Ariko n’aho igipolisi kijejwe inyifato kiriko kirasamburwa ntibisigura ko iri tegeko rimaze imyaka mirongo rizoca rihinduka
 Imyiyerekano irongowe n’abagore, yiswe “imigumuko” n’abategetsi, ikwiragiye muri Irani kuva Amini  yari afise imyaka 22 apfiriye mu gasho ku wa 16 z’ukw’icenda, inyuma y’imisi itatu ahagaritswe n’igipolisi kijejwe inyifato ku mugwa mukuru Tehran
 Urupfu rwiwe rwabaye intandaro y’aka kaguma ariko kandi rwaje rukurikira uburakari bwari busanzwe mu gihugu butewe n’ubukene, ubushomeri, ubusumbasumbane, akarenganyo n’igiturire
 Mu gihe vyokwemezwa, isamburwa ry’igipolisi kijejwe inyifato ryoba ryerekana ko ubutegetsi bwemeye impinduka ariko nta cemeza ko ico conyene coba kimaze kugira ngo imyiyerekano ihagarare, aho abari muri yo bagiye baturira ibitambara vyo kwitwikira mu mutwe
 Mu kiganiro Newshour ca BBC, umugore umwe w’umunya-Irani yavuze ati: "Kubona reta yafashe ingingo yo gusenyura igipolisi kijejwe inyifato ntibisigura ko imyiyerekano ihagaze
 "N’aho reta yovuga ko kwambara hijab ari ku gushaka kw’umuntu ntibihagije
 Abanyagihugu barazi ko ata kazoza ka Irani igifise reta nk’iyi ku butegetsi
 “Tugiye kubona ingene abanyagihugu b’ingeri zitandukanye za Irani, baba ba ntahompagaze canke abakigendera ku mico ya kera, baza gushigikira abagore bariko bararwanira uburenganzira bwabo”
 Uwundi mugore nawe ati: "Twebwe, abari mu myiyerekano, ntitukirajwe ishinga na hijab
 Tumaze imisi 70 dutembera tutayambaye
 "Tubona impinduka
 Hijab niyo yabaye intango kandi nta kindi dushaka kindi atari urupfu rw’umukuru w’igihugu atwaza umukazo n’ihinduka ry’ubutegetsi”
 Ibinyamakuru vya reta ya Irani vyahakanye amakuru avuga ko igipolisi kijejwe inyifato kiriko kirasaburwa, nk’uko bivugwa na CNN
 Imboneshakure ya reta Al-Alam yoba yatangaje ko ibinyamakuru vyo mu mahanga vyerekana ko amajambo ya Montazeri avuga ko "Irani yasubije umugongo inyuma ku kibazo ca hijab n’ukwicisha bugufi, kandi ko vyavuye ku migumuko iheruka”
 "Ariko nta mutegetsi n’umwe wa Irani aratangaza ko igipolisi kijejwe inyifato casambuwe”
 Umushikiranganji wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire Antony Blinken avuga ko ari nka hamwe Irani yosambura igipolisi kijejwe inyifato coba ari “ikintu ciza” anashimagiza “ubutwari budasanzwe bw’urwaruka rwa Irani, cane cane abagore, bafashe iya mbere muri ino myiyerekano”
 Blinken avuga ati: "Nimba ubutegetsi hari ukuntu bwishuye ibisabwa muri iyo myiyerekano, iki coba ari ikintu ciza”
 Kuva habaye impinduka za ki-Islam mu 1979 muri Irani, iki gihugu cagiye kigira integuro zitandukanye z’“igipolisi kijejwe inyifato”, ariko ikiriho ubu – kizwi nka Gasht-e Ershad – nico nyamukuru muri kino gihe kijejwe guhagararira ikurikizwa ry’itegeko rya Islam rijejwe inyifato muri Irani
 Catanguye gukizura mu 2006 mu ntumbero yo kwubahiriza ibwirizwa rigenga inyambaro, ritegeka abagore kwambara impuzu ndende rikabuza kwambara ikaburuta, amajinisi (jeans) atabaguye hamwe n’izindi mpuzu zifatwa ko zitiyubashe

