N﻿a Damian Zane BBC News Abantu 14 muri Afrika y’Epfo barapfuye bahitanywe n’umwuzure wateye uruzi bariko bagiriramwo ibirori vy’urusengero rwabo
 Ku wa gatandatu, bamwe mu banyeshengero barenga 30 bari bahagaze ku mabuye y’urutare igihe umukuba w’amazi wabatera giturumbuka, nk’uko ababibonye babivuga
 Umupasitori yakijijwe n’ishami ry’igiti yafashe akaryizirikako mu gihe nawe nyene yariko aratwarwa, nk’uko uyu yabibonye abivuga
 Kuwa mungu mugoroba, abajejwe ubutabazi bari bahagaritse ibikorwa vyo kurondera aboba bakiri muri urwo ruzi Jukskei  ruri i Johannesburg
 Haracibazwa ko nibura abantu batatu bataramenyekana amaherezo yabo kandi igikorwa co kubarondera gisanzwe kiriko kirakorwa n’igipolisi hamwe n’igisata kijejwe kuzimya imiriro y’ivyaduka be n’abahinga mu kurokora abatwawe n’inzuzi, kirabandanya kuri uno wa mbere
 Inyuma yo gutora ibiziga bibiri ku wa gatandatu, ejo ku wa Mungu batoye ibindi 12, nk’uko Robert Mulaudzi, umuvugizi w’igisata kijejwe ubutabazi c’igisagara ca Johannesburg, yabibwiye abanyamakuru
 Imbere y’aha, yavuze ko abategetsi bari bagabishije abanyagihugu ko bokwiyubara mu gihe bokorera ibirori muri urwo ruzi canke hafi yarwo, uruzi ruzwi ko rukunze guterwa n’imyuzure mu gihe c’imvura muri Afrika y’Epfo
 "Abanyagihugu bacu, cane cane abasenga bakora imigirwa nk’iyo, bazokwipfuza kuja muri izi nzuzi
 Ubutumwa tubaha ni uko bokwiyubara mu gihe bari muri iyi migirwa”
 Victor Ncube, nawe yari muri ico gisabisho, yabwiye ikinyamakuru co muri ico gihugu, eNCA, ko yashoboye kurokora abantu batanu akabakura muri urwo ruzi bari bamaze gutwara gushika ku metero 100
 Avuga ko abandi rwari rwabagejeje kure ku buryo atari gushikayo ngo agerageze kubarokora

Abashakashatsi bafashe amasanamu y’ibibera mu mihogo y’uduhungarema, basanga ivyo dukora bihuye n’ubuhinga abaririmvyi bakoresha mu gusohora amajwi arenga
 Uduhungarema turashobora gusohora imikuba itandukanye y’amajwi (frequencies), irenga kure aho ijwi ry’umuntu rishobora kugera
 Uduhungarema dushobora gushikana amajwi yatwo ku rugero rwa 'octaves' indwi, mu gihe umuntu we atarenza 'octaves' zitatu
 Uru rupimo rwa 'Octave' rushingiye ku mwanya w'urukurikirane rw’imirya, uri hagati y’umurya n’uwundi bisa ariko mw’ijwi ritari ku rugero rumwe
 Nko ku gitari canke piyano, amajwi aba atonze nk’akarorero ku ma 'notes'- CDEFGAB-CDEFGAB- CDEFGAB- gutyo gutyo izi zikaba ari nka 'Octaves' zitatu
 N’ukuvuga amajwi indwi kuva aho 'note' ya mbere ihera n’aho isubira gutangurira ikaza igira munani muri urwo rukurikirane
 Aha ni naho havuye iryo zina rya ‘octave’ kuko igiharuro ‘umunani’ mu rurimi rw’iki latini ari ‘Octo’
 Abashakashatsi bavuga ko kubona amajwi y’uduhungarema ashobora gushika kuri 'octaves' indwi ari ibintu bitangaje
 Abo bashakashatsi bavuga ko bamwe mu baririmvyi nka Mariah Carey bashobora gushikana ijwi kuri 'octaves' zine canke zitanu
 Ntibashoboye mugabo gutahura mu buryo bwuzuye insiguro ya zimwe mu ndirimbo z’utwo duhungarema canke amajwi yatwo
 Ariko barashoboye kumenya ko turamukanya mu majwi kandi bamenya n’uko duhinyanyura ayo majwi
 Professor Coen Elemans, yigisha muri kaminuza ya Southern Denmark, ari nawe yayoboye ico gikorwa, avuga ko babonye ubwa mbere ‘uko imirya yo mu mihogo ihindura ija imbere yongera isubira inyuma, muri utwo duhungarema mu gusohora amajwi atandukanye
 Agira ati: “Nk’akarorero, mu gusohora ijwi ryo hasi turiko turahamagarana, dukoresha imirya yitwa 'false vocal folds' – nk’uko n’abaririmvyi babikora"
 Izo ‘false vocal folds’ n’imitsi y’umuhogo canke imirya umuntu adakenera gukoresha mu gihe ariko aravuga canke aririmba bisanzwe
 Bisanzwe bizwi ko abaririmvyi basakuza cane bamwe bavuza umuziki umena amatwi bita ‘metal singers’ ari bo bakoresha imirya y’umuhogo ya ‘false vocal folds’ nk’utwo duhungarema
 Mariah Carey ni umuririmvyi wo muri Leta zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, yamenyekanye cane kubera indirimbo ziwe za Noweli, harimwo urwakunzwe kurusha izindi mu Bwongereza mu zo mu bwoko bwa ‘classics’: 'All I Want for Christmas is You'
 Yayiririmbanye mu birori na Justin Bieber mu 2011, ariko yari yasohotse ubwa mbere mu 1994
 Mariah, azwi kubera ubushobozi bwiwe bwo guhibongoza, yaririmvye indirimbo z’ubwoko bwinshi zirimwo iza Pop, R&B, Hip-hop na Soul

N﻿a Leire Ventas B﻿BC Mundo, Los Angeles Ubu wanduye   umugera wa Sida, ntibikiri nko kuba uciriwe urubanza rwo gupfa nk’uko vyari bimeze mu myaka mirongo iheze, kuko ubu ushobora kubaho ubuzima busanzwe
 Ubu nibwo butumwa bukomeye mw’umwizero butangwa n’abari mu gisata kijejwe kurwanya uyu mugera wa VIH utera indwara ya Sida
 Kuva hamenyekanye abantu ba mbere banduye iyo ndwara mu myaka ya 1980, abantu barenga imiriyoni 40 baramaze  gupfa bahitanywe n’indwara zifitaniye isano n’uwo mugera, hamwe n’indwara iterwa nawo, izwi nka Sida
 Mu mwaka uheze wonyene, iyo ndwara yahitanye abantu 450
000, imiriyoni 1,5 nabo barandura umugera wayo, nk’uko biri mu biharuro bitangwa n’ishami rya ONU rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi OMS/WHO
 Urwo rwego ruvuga ko imiriyoni 38,4 kw’isi bagendana umugera, 2/3 bakaba baba ku mugabane wa Afrika
 Ubu, uburyo bwo gupima umugera hakiri kare bwararwiriye, imiti nayo iriyongera kandi igashikira abayikeneye
 Hari n’ibihugu biri hafi yo kuwutuza burundu
 David Goodman-Meza  umwigisha wa kaminuza,  abwira BBC ati:  "Tumaze imyaka 40 dukora ubushakashatsi, kandi, n’aho ata rucanco dufise, hari intambwe zikomeye zimaze gushikwako mu kurwanya uwu mugera, kuwuvura no gukomeza amagara y’abamaze kuwandura”
 None ni izihe ntambwe nyamukuru zitatu zoba zimaze guterwa zigatanga n’umwizero mu rugamba rwo kurwanya iki kiza? Umugera wa SDA, ari wo VIH, utera abasoda b’umubiri ukabaka  inguvu zo gushobora kurwanya izindi ndwara zitari nke, harimwo n’ubwoko bumwe bumwe bwa kanseri (cancer) umubiri w’umuntu wari ushoboye kurwanya mu buryo bworoshe
 Iyi ngorane irashobora gutorerwa umuti n’imiti yo gupfupfahaza, izwi nka Antiretroviral therapy canke ART mu mpfunyapfunyo
 Kuva mu 2016, OMS yategetse ko abo bose banduye umugera wa SIDA bahabwa ART ubuzima bwabo bwose, harimwo abana, imiyabaga n’abagore bibungenze ata kuraba nimba hari izndi ndwara bariko barivuza
 Ibi vyatumye mu mwaka uheze, abantu imiriyoni 28,7 banduye umugera kw’isi bahabwa iyi miti ipfupfahaza
 Iyi miti ntabwo ivura uwu mugera, ariko ituma utiyongera mu mubiri bigatuma abasoda b’umubiri bagira inguvu zo kurwanya izindi ngwara
 Ayako Miyashita  wo mu kigo ca California c’ubushakashatsi ku mugera wa SIDA, (California HIV/AIDS Policy Research Centers, CHPRC) avuga ati: "Vyongeye, ico twize muri ino myaka ya vuba ni uko iyo umuti ufashwe neza ugabanya ivyago vyo gukwiragiza umugera ku rugero rwa 100%”
 Avuga ati: "Iyo umugera udashobora kuboneka mu mubiri w’umuntu, ni uko aba adashobora kuwanduza ku muntu wundi n’umwe”
 Iki rero ni ikintu gikomeye cane, atari mu kurwanya iyi ndwara gusa, ariko kandi no kurwanya inenwa ku bagendana umugera”
 Avuga kandi ko muri ino myaka ya vuba habaye intambwe “zidasanzwe” mu bijanye n’ubwo buvuzi
 Umwigisha wa kaminuza Goodman-Meza  avuga ati: "Ibintu vyarahindutse cane kuva mu myaka ya 1990 canke 2000, aho abarwayi bategerezwa gufata imiti myinshi ku musi umwe n’ingaruka yabagirako”
 Ubu ni ikinini kimwe gusa ku musi kandi nta ngaruka nini kibagirako
 Kandi ubushakashatsi burabandanya muri iki gisata, barondera ubuvuzi bw’igihe kirekire
 Mu mwaka uheze, ikigo ca Amerika kijejwe kugenzura imiti n’imfungurwa (Food and Drug Administration, FDA) caremeje umuti wa mbere ukora igihe kirekire, urushinge rw’imiti ibiri umuntu aterwa rimwe mu mezi abiri
 Miyashita  ashimangira ati: "Iyumvire ico bisigura nko ku muntu yari amaze imyaka mirongo ari ku binini vya misi yose”
 Kuri Suzi Steward w’imyaka 62 agendana umugera wa Sida kuva mu 2006, nico kintu ca mbere gikomeye cabaye kuri we mu myaka 15
 Yabaye mu murwi wageragerejweko uwo muti, mbere igihe yemererwa kuba muri uwo murwi yararize kubera umunezero
 Yabwiye ikinyamakuru gitangaza amakuru ku bijanye n’amagara y’abantu, Healthline,  ati: "Ni ukuri nari ndushe n’ibinini biguma binyibutsa ingwara yanje imisi yose”
 Hari kandi n’ubushakashatsi buriko burakorwa ku miti yohabwa abantu imibiri yabo itakira iyi miti yo gupfupfahaza
 "Hari intambwe zikomeye zatewe mu kuvura uwu mugera, ariko ikintu nyaco gikomeye kiri mu rwego rwo gukinga”, niko  Miyashita  wo mu kigo CHPRC avuga
 Aha ashaka kuvuga umuti uzwi nka prophylaxie pré-exposition/ pre-exposure prophylaxis, uzwi mu mpfunyapfunyo nka PrEP
 Mu gihe PrEP ifashwe imisi yose, ishobora kugabanya ivyago vyo kwandura umugera utera Sida uciye mu guhuza ibitsina ku rugero rwa 90% canke 70% biciye mw’ikoreshwa ry’inshinge canke ibikoresho bindi bitobora uruhu bidatunganye, nk’uko bivugwa n’ikigo ca Amerika kijejwe kugenzura indwara, Centers for the Disease Control and Prevention (CDC)
 Ikompanyi ya Amerika ihingura imiti, Gilead Sciences, yatanguye kuyigurisha mu 2012 yitwa Truvada
 Haciye imyaka itatu, OMS yaciye itangura gusaba ko yokoreshwa mu gukinga umugera wa Sida ku mirwi y’abantu bari mu vyago vyinshi vyo gushobora kuwandura , nk’abahuza ibitsina babisangiye, ababeshejweho n’ubumaraya, canke abafise abakunzi banduye umugera
 Ariko rero, n’aho mu bihugu biteye imbere habonekamwo akarusho, uturere tubangamiwe cane gusumba utundi nta nyungu ibonekamwo kubera igiciro cayo kiri hejuru
 Goodman-Meza  avuga ko n’imiti y’urushinge imara igihe kirekire iherutse kwemezwa
 Aha ashaka kuvuga nk’akarorero ku muti w’urushinge uriko urageragerezwa muri Afrika y’Epfo wagiye kuboneka ko ari intambwe ikomeye: watumye abariko bawugeragerezwako bagira amahirwe manini yo kutandura umugera wa Sida ku rugero rwa 88% gusumba ibinini bariko barafata imisi yose
 Muri ino myaka ya vuba, urugero rw’abandura rwaragabanutse, umuti wa PrEP uterwa mu rushinge ukaba ari wo muti wa mbere ufise akamaro kanini mu kwirinda umugera wa Sida igihe kirekire
 Inyuma y’imyaka hafi 40 y’ubushakashatsi, nta rucanco rwa SIDA rurashobora kuboneka
 Iziriko zirageragezwa ziracari ku rugero rwo hasi cane
 Anthony S
 Fauci yahoze ari umukuru w’ikigo kijejwe kurwanya indwara z’uguhuganirwa n’izandukira, National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases (NIAID), ubu akaba ari umuhanuzi w’umukuru w’igihugu mu vyo amagara y’abantu, avuga ati: " Gutora urucanco rwa SIDA biboneka ko kikiri ikibazo c’ingorabahizi”
 "Inyuma y’aho dutoreye incanco nyazo za Covid-19, turafise amahirwe menshi yo kuraba uno musi nimba twoshika ku ntambwe nk’iyo mu kurwanya umugera wa SIDA”
 Miyashita  ati: "Muri iki gihe, nta rucanco turaronka, kandi nta n’umuti turaronka”
 Nivyo ko hari abantu bazwi ko bashoboye gukira, canke n’imiburiburi bakamara amezi atari make badafise umugera
 Ariko ibi ni ivyavuye mu buvuzi n’amagerageza bishasha bitoroshe gukoresha ku bantu banduye
 Uyu muhinga ashimangira ati: "Kimwe mu bintu tudashobora kwibagira ni uko hari abantu bagendana umugera wa SIDA ubu kandi mu gihe tuzoba tutarashika kuri iyo ntambwe yo kuronka, atari urucanco gusa, ariko kandi n’umuti, turacafise igikorwa gikomeye imbere yacu”
 Hanyuma kandi, ntitwibagire ko atari ibihugu vyose bifise ubushobozi bwo kuronka ibiva muri ubu buhinga
 "Uburinganire ku magara no kuvurwa neza ni ikintu kitarashikwako kw’isi
 Rero iterambere muri ubwo buhinga mu vyo amagara y’abantu ntaco rivuze
 Mu gihe tudashitse ku rugero rw’aho bose bazoba bashobora kuronka ubwo buryo, ntiturote twibaza ko umugera wa SIDA tuzoshobora kuwutuza”

