N﻿a Bernd Debusmann Jr BBC News, Washington Mu gihe harangwa icuka kibi, kw’isi ibintu bimeze nabi, urukino rwaheruka hagati ya Irani na Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika mu 1998 rwatangujwe n’ikimenyetso kidasanzwe – amashurwe yera
 Aya mashurwe, nk’uko umumenyereza wa Irani ico gihe yabivuze, cari ikimenyetso c’amahoro imbere y’urukino rwahuje ibi bihugu mu Bufaransa
 Imyaka 20 inyuma y’aha, icuka kibi carasubiye kurenga urugero imbere y’urukino rwa nijoro hagati ya Iran na Amerika muri Qatar
 Hagati aho, uru rukino rwabaye ata kimentetso na kimwe c’ubugenzi
 Urukino rw’imbere y’aha rwabereye muri Lyon, rwabaye inyuma y’imyaka 20 imigenderanire hagati y’ibi bihugu bibiri yarabaye nabi cane nk’inkurikizi z’iturirwa ry’ibiro vy’ubuserukizi bwa Amerika i Tehran mu 1979
 Ryakurikiwe n’ikibazo catewe n’abanyeshure, bahagarikiwe n’ubutegetsi bwa Ayatollah Khomeini, bafashe bugwati abakozi bo muri ubwo buserukizi mu kiringo c’imisi 444
 Ico gihe, ukwezi kumwe gusa imbere y’urwo rukino, ubushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire bwa Amerika bwise Irani ko ari co gihugu ca mbere kw’isi cafata mu mugongo iterabwoba, mu gihe abategetsi batari bake ba Irani batahengeshanya gushikiriza amajambo arwanya Amerika
