 Ntituri ng’aha ngo turwane canke dukore ikindi kintu ico ari co cose”
 Mu kubasubiriza mu ndumane, abakinyi ba Amerika babahaye utudarapo tw’ishirahamwe rya Amerika rijejwe umupira w’amagugu  (US Soccer Federation, USSF)
 Abakinyi b’iyi mirwi yompi bari kumwe bifotoreje hamwe mw’ifoto rusangi bamwenyura imbere y’uru rukino rwari rukomeye
 Muri iyo nkuru ya ESPN, Cobi Jones  yakina hagati mu murwi wa Amerika avuga ati: "Nibaza ko kirya cari ikintu gikomeye
 "Kwari nk’ukwerekana ko inkino ziri hejuru ya poritike n’ivyo bindi vyose
 Cari ikintu gikomeye, hanyuma no kwifotoreza hamwe navyo biza birushirizaho”
 Imisi mikeya imbere y’uru rukino rundi rwo mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi nijoro ku wa kabiri hagati y’iyi mirwi ibiri, hasubiye kwaduka ikindi cuka kibi, mu gihe Irani ihanganye n’imyiyerekano y’abiyamiriza reta, mu gihe kandi USSF yari ihejeje gukura ikimenyetso c’iki gihugu kigendera kw’idini rya Islam kw’ibendera, mu nkuru y’amasanamu yari yashize ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi
 Aya masanamu yahavuye afutwa, umumenyereza wa Amerika nawe, Gregg Berhalter, aca asaba imbabazi , avuga ko “rimwe na rimwe hari ibintu bigoye gukontorora”, kandi ko we n’umurwi wa Amerika barajwe ishinga n’umupira w’amaguru
 Amerika yinjiye mu kibuga yizeye ko idasubira gukubitwa nk’uko vyagenze mu  1998 rwarangiye itsinzwe na Irani 2-1, n’aho ibi bihugu vyompi bitashoboye kubandanya ihiganwa inyuma y’urwo rukino
 Alexi Lalas, umunyamakuru wa Fox Sports yari mu murwi wakinye urwo rukino rwa 1998, yabwiye ikinyamakuru Associated Press ko umurwi nserukiragihugu wa Amerika wa kino gihe wategerezwa kuja mu kibuga wagabishijwe ko cazira kwirengagiza insiguro ya poritike y’uru rukino
 Mu kwerekana igituma Amerika idategerezwa gufyinata mu kibuga, avuga ati: “Gutahura akamaro k’uru rukino, atari kuraba gusa ku ruhande rw’umupira w’amaguru bagafatira ahubwo ku muco, nibaza ko ari ikintu gikomeye kuri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika”
 Urukino rwa nijoro hagati ya Amerika na Iran muri Qatar rwarangiye Amerika itsinze Irani 1-0 ku gitsindo ca Christian Pulisic ku munota wa 38

