Inama nkenguzamateka ya Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yemeje integuro y’itegeko rikingira abubakanye basangiye ibitsina hamwe n’abubakanye badasangiye amoko
 Iri tegeko rica risubira mu nama nshingamateka yiteze kuryemeza hanyuma ice irirungikira umukuru w’igihugu Biden kugira ngo aritereko igikumu
 Abashigikiye iri tegeko bizeye ko ryemezwa imbere y’uko Abarepubulika bafata Inama nshingamateka mu kwa mbere
 Hagati aho, iyi nteguro ntitegeka intara zose mu gihugu gushingira abubakana basangiye igitsina
 Integuro y’iri tegeko yagiye kuronka inguvu inyuma y’aho, mu kwa gatandatu, Sentare nkuru y’igihugu ifatiye icemezo igafuta uburenganzira bwo gukorora inda bwatangwa n’igihugu
 Abaharanira agateka k’abari muri wa murwi w’abahuza ibitsina babisangiye (LGBT) bafise ubwoba ko uburenganzira bwo kurongorana hagati y’abasangiye igitsina bushobora kugwa mu ngorane mu mezi ari imbere
 Abemeje iyi nteguro mu matora yabaye nijoro ku wa kabiri ni 61 kuri 36 ,aho Abarepubulika 12 bayemeje
 Iyi nteguro yagiye gushigikirwa n’abakenguzamateka b’Abarepubulika inyuma y’aho yongewemwo ingingo zikingira ubwigenge bw’amadini
 Integuro y’iri tegeko ifise intumbero yo gushimangira uburenganzira bw’abarongorana basangiye ibitsina mu mategeko y’igihugu, n’aho ababana muri iyo nzira basanzwe bakingiwe mu gihugu biciye mu ngingo Sentare nkuru y’igihugu yafashe imbere y’aha
 Mw’itangazo, umukuru wa nyarwinshi mu nama nkenguzamateka Chuck Schumer arashimagiza iyi ngingo, akavuga ko ari intambwe ikomeye “mu rugendo rurerure rutera ruja ku buringanire nyabwo”
 "Mu kwemeza iyi nteguro, inama nkenguzamateka irungitse ubutumwa buri munyamerika akeneye kwumva: Ata kuraba uwo uri canke uwo ukunda, na wewe ukeneye iteka no gufatwa kumwe nk’abandi imbere y’amategeko”
 Tammy Baldwin, umukenguzamateka wa mbere w’umu-Democrat yavyiyemeje ku mugaragaro, akongera agafata iya mbere mu rugamba rwo guharanira iyi nteguro, avuga ko iri tegeko “rizokingira intambwe yashitsweko bigoranye” ku burenganzira bw’abubakana basangiye ibitsina muri Amerika
 Iyi nteguro nshasha ikuraho ku mugaragaro itegeko rikingira ugushingira, rizwi nka Defense of Marriage Act (DOMA) ryo mu 1996 risigura neza ko ukurongorana biba gusa hagati y’umugabo n’umugore
 Mu 2013, Sentare nkuru y’igihugu yafashe ingingo yavuga ko iri tegeko riteye kubiri n’ibwirizwashingiro
 Integuro y’iri tegeko yaraye yemejwe n’inama nkenguzamateka isaba kandi intara kwemera abubakanye basangiye ibitsina bashingiraniye mu zindi ntara
 Isaba kandi intara gukora ku buryo abubakanye basangiye ibitsina baronswa uburenganzira butangwa n’igihugu
 Aya matora yabaye inyuma y’ibiganiro hagati y’imigambwe yompi iri mu nama nkenguzamateka vyamaze amezi atari make, akaba kandi abaye inyuma y’amatora aheruka yo hagati muri manda, akaba ahumuriza bamwe mu bakenguzamateka

Malawi yatanguye isekeza ryo gukingira ku bwinshi  abana malaria mu kubaha urucanco rw’iyo ndwara, kikaba arico gikorwa ca mbere nk’ico kw’isi, nk’uko bivugwa na  Muganga Dr Neema Kimambo aserukira muri ico gihugu ishami rya ONU riraba amagara kw’isi, OMS
 Aho muri Malawi hariko harakoreshwa urucanco  rumwe rwonyene rumaze kwemezwa na OMS
 Urwo rucanco ruzwi nka RTS,S rwarageragejwe incuro nyinshi mu bihugu vya Malawi, Ghana na Kenya muri iyi myaka mike iheze
 Mw’igeragezwa ryarwo rya vuba kuva mu 2019, OMS yafashije mw’icandagwa  ry’abana 360
000 ku mwaka  muri ivyo bihugu bitatu
 Iryo geragezwa ryerekanye ko mu bahawe urwo rucanco, 30% y’abana bafise hagati y’amezi 5 n’amezi 17 baronka ubudahangarwa
 Urwo rugero ruri hasi rw’ingene urwo rucanco rukingira vyatumye hari abibaza niba koko bokwirirwa bararurondera
 Ishirahamwe Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation risanzwe rishigikira gukora incanco, nta ruhara rutaziguye rifise mu gushigikira iryo sekeza ryatanguye muri Malawi kuko ryibaza ko  vyoba vyiza gusumba gushira amafaranga mu bundi buryo bwo kurwanya malaria hamwe n’izindi ncanco ziriko ziratunganywa, nk’uko bivugwa n’urubuga Devex
 RTS,S rwa kompanyi ikora imiti ya GSK (GlaxoSmithKlein) rwari rumaze imyaka 30 ruhingurwa
 N’aho urwo rucanco rufise urugero ruri hasi rwo gukinga, rwatumye hiyongera icizere co kubuza gupfa bamwe mu bantu 400
000 bahitanwa buri mwaka n’iyo ndwara ikwiragizwa n’imibu, benshi muri abo  akaba ari abo muri Afrika
 Mu 2020, abantu barenga miriyoni 4 muri Malawi barafashwe na malaria, kandi kuri abo barenga 2
500, cane cane bafise munsi y’imyaka itanu, vyaremejwe ko bishwe n’iyo ndwara
 Uwujejwe igisata co kurwanya malaria muri ico goihugu, Muganga  Michael Kayange, yabwiye ikiganiro Focus on Africa  ca BBC ko urwo rucanco ubu ruzobuza zimwe muri izo mpfu
 Ati: ‘’Turazi neza ko rufise urugero ruto cane rwo gukora… (ariko) mu kurwanya malaria, nta buryo na bumwe buhari bushobora vyose
 Ntituriko turavuga ngo urwo rucanco rwa malaria ruje kuyizimanganya burundu, ariko ni bumwe mu buryo bwo kuyizimanganya’’
 Izindi ngingo zirimwo gutanga imisegetera irimwo umuti yo kwikingira imibu iyo abantu baryamye
 Urwo rucanco ruzotangwa mu gihugu cose
 Muganga Kayange yavuze ko abana bose bafise munsi y’imyaka itanu, aho bari hose, bazotegerzwa kururonka
 Urwo rucanco rutangwa kane - rimwe buri kwezi mu mezi atatu ya mbere hanyuma irya kane haheze amezi 18

