 Papa François yabwiye ikinyamakuru co muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ko ingabo “z’abagome” mu bisanzwe ni aba Chechens n’aba Buryats
 Yavuze kandi ko ikigoyi kizwi nka Holodomor catewe na Kremlin muri Ukraine mu myaka ya 1930 ko ari ihonyabwoko
 Uburusiya buvuga ko aya majambo ari ayo “gusambura”, bukavuga ko amoko yose ari mu gihugu agize “umuryango umwe”
 Mu kiganiro America, ikinyamakuru c’umuhari w’aba Jesuites, Papa François yabajijwe igituma ahigitanya kwiyamiriza adahigimanga Uburusiya kubera iyi ntambara
 Mu kwishura, avuga ko yahawe “amakuru menshi yerekeye ubugome bw’ingabo”
