 Mu gisa n’inyishu ku vyo yagirizwa vy’uko atiyamiriza Perezida Putin mu buryo butaziguye, avuga ati: “Rimwe na rimwe ngerageza kutadomako urutoke kugira ngo ntihagire uwo mbabaza ariko nkiyamiriza muri rusangi, n’aho bizwi neza uwo mba ndiko ndiyamiriza
 Si ngombwa ko ndamuvuga izina”
 Mu nyuma, muri ico kiganiro, Papa yavuze ati: “Nta numwe atazi aho mpagaze, ndi kumwe na Putin canke ntari kumwe na we, ntarinze kuvuga izina ryiwe”
 Maria Zakharova  avugira ubushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire bw’Uburusiya ariyamiriza ayo majambo nk’uko bivugwa n’ikinyamakuru RT cegamiye reta
