Na Yogita Limaye BBC News, Herat A﻿banya-Afghanistan basigaye baha imiti abana babo kugira babasinzirize - abandi bagurisha abakobwa babo n'ingingo z'umubiri kugira babe baramaze kabiri
 Ku gihe  c'imbeho (hiver/winter) kigira kabiri kuva aba-Taliban bagarutse ku butegetsi hanyuma imfashanyo ziva hanze zigahagarikwa,  abaharurwa muri za miriyoni bugarijwe n'inzara
 A﻿bdul Wahab avuga ati: "Abana bacu baguma barira, kandi ntibasinzira
 Nta vyo kurya dufise
" "﻿Duca tuja kuri farumasi, tukazana ibini tugaha abana bacu kugira bashobore gutora itiro
" U﻿wo mugabo aba mu nkengera za Herat, igisagara kiza ubugira gatatu mu bunini muri ico gihugu, mu kigwati  c'utuzu duto duto tw'ivyondo cagiye kiraguka kuva mu myaka iheze, kikuzura abantu bomowe n'intambara n'ibindi biza vyizana
 A﻿bdul ari mu mugwi w'abantu hafi 10 baje begera aho turi
 Twarababajije, tuti ni bangahe baha imiti abana babo kugira babasinzirize?  Nabo bishura bati: "Benshi, twese"
 Ghulam Hazrat  yaciye akora mu mufuko wiwe asokorora agapfungo k'ibinini
  Vyari ibinini vya  alprazolam - ibinini ku bisanzwe bihabwa abantu baba bafise ingorane z'umwitwarariko mwinshi
 Ghulam afise abana batandatu, umuto muri bo afise umwaka umwe
 Ati: "Nawe nyene ndamuha"
 Abandi batweretse ibinini vya escitalopram na sertraline bavuze ko baha abana babo
 Ivyo navyo ku bisanzwe vyandikirwa abayinze n'abafise umwitwarariko mwinshi
 A﻿baganga bavuga ko iyo ihawe abana bakiri bato kandi bataronka ivyo kurya bihagije, imiti bene iyo yonona igitigu (umwijima mu kinyarwanda), igatera 'izindi ngorane nyinshi nko kwama ufise uburuhe, n'ihungabana ryo gusinzira n'inyifato
 K﻿uri farumasi imwe, twasanze ushobora kugura ibinini bitanu vy'iyo miti ikoreshwa ku ma Afghani (amafaranga yo muri Afgnistan) 10, (nka 200 mu mafaranga y'Uburundi), ayagura ikimanyu c'umukate
 Myinshi mu miryango twahuye yasangira ibimanyu bikeye vy'imikate buri munsi
 Umugore umwe yatubwiye ko bari bariye umukate wumye mu gitondo, mw'ijoro naho bakuwudumba mu mazi kugira worohe
 O﻿NU ivuga ko ubu "akaga" kariko karaba muri Afghanistan
 Abagabo benshi mu karere kari ku nkengera ya Herat bakora ibikonkwano vyo ku munsi mu mirima
 Bamaze imyaka babayeho ubuzima bugoye
