 K﻿u munsi bagize igihamana bakaronka akazi, baca nk'ama Afghani 100 (ni ibihumbi bibiri birenga gato mu mafaranga y'Uburundi)
 A﻿ho twagiye hose twasanze abantu bafata ingingo zikomeye cane kugira imiryango yabo ntiyicwe n'inzara
 Ammar (siryo zina ryiwe ry'ukuri) yavuze ko yabazwe kugira bamukuremwo ifyigo haraheze amezi atatu aca aratwereka n'inkovu ndende y'aho babaze - n'ahaciye inyuzi hagitukura - kuva mu kaziba k'inda utera uja mu mugongo
 A﻿ri mu myaka ya 20, yategerezwa kuba  ari mu myaka iryoshe y'ubuzima bwiwe
 Twanyegeje umwidondoro wiwe kugira tumukingire
 Y﻿avuze ati: "Nta kundi nari kugira
 Numvise ko ushobora kugurisha ifyigo ku bitaro vya hano
 Nca ndajayo hanyuma ndababwira ko nshaka [kurigurisha]
 Haheze amayinga make, naciye nvumva bampamagaye bansaba kuja ku bitaro
" "﻿Barakoze ibipimo bikeya, hanyuma bantera umuti watumye ntasubira kumenya ubwenge
