 A﻿ma-Afghani 240
000 (miriyoni hafi 5,5 mu marundi) yaronse kuri iryo fyigo ntakwiye
 "﻿Ubu nta kundi turi bugire atari ukugurisha umwana wacu w'umukobwa w'imyaka ibiri
