 "﻿Ndamaramazwa cane n'aho tugeze
 Rimwe na rimwe numva ari vyiza gupfa kuruta kubaho gutya," ivyo navyo bivugwa n'umugabo wiwe
 Kenshi cane, twarumvise inkuru z'abagurisha abakobwa babo
 Nizamuddin ati: "Naragurishije umukobwa wanje w'imyaka itanu ku ma Afghani 100
000
" A﻿yo ntashika ayo ifyigo rigurwa, nk'uko twabibonye
 U﻿bu agateka k'abantu b'aha mu kubaho karatabagajwe n'inzara
 A﻿bdul Ghafar, umwe mu ndongozi z'aho ati: "Turumva ko biteye kubiri n'amategeko ya Islam kandi ko dushira ubuzima bw'abana bacu mu kaga, ariko nta yindi nzira ihari
"  M﻿u rugo rumwe twahasanze Nazia, akana k'agakobwa k'imyaka ine kariko karakina kagira utugugu na Shamshullah, musazawe w'amezi 18
