" N﻿azia yaragurishijwe ngo arongorwe n'umuhungu wo mu muryango wo mu ntara yo mu bumanuko ya Kandahar
 Ku mwaka 14 azoca arungikwa
 Gushika ubu Hazratullah amaze kwakira kabiri amafaranga yo kumugura
 Hazratullah avuga ko menshi muri ayo mafaranga yakoreshejwe mu kugura ivyo kurya, ayandi imiti y'umuhungu wiwe muto
