Reta Zunze Ubmwe za Amerika yabujije kugurisha no kwinjiza ibikoresho vy’amakompanyi atanu y’Ubushinwa, harimwo Huawei na ZTE, ku mvo z’umutekano w’igihugu
 Ayandi makompanyi ari kuri uru rutonde ni Hikvision, Dahua na Hytera ahingura ibikoresho vya ya ma camera yo gucungera (video surveillance) hamwe na ya maradio yo guhanahana amakuru
 Ni bwo bwa mbere abategetsi ba Amerika bafashe ingingo nk’iyi ku mvo z’umutekano
 Hikvision ivuga ko ibikoresho vyayo ata ngorane z’umutekano biteje kuri Amerika
 Ivuga ko iyi ngingo ata “kintu na kimwe izofasha ku mutekano wa Amerika, ariko ko izokwonona vyinshi kandi ko izoba uruhombo ku badandaza bato bato, abategetsi bo hasi, abarongoye amashure ku nzego z’uturere hamwe n’abantu ku giti cabo muri Amerika, mu twigoro twabo two kwikingira, gukingira imihana yabo, udurandaza rwabo n’amatungo yabo”
 Huawei n’ayandi makompanyi aherutse guhakana ko ata makuru ahereza reta y’Ubushinwa
 Umurwi w’igihugu ujejwe guhanahana amakuru muri Amerika (Federal Communications Commission, FCC) uvuga ko abawugize bemeje nijoro ku wa gatanu ata n’umwe avuyemwo izo ngingo nshasha
 Jessica Rosenworcel  arogoye uyo murwi avuga mw’itangazo ati: "FCC yariyemeje gukingira umutekano w’igihugu cacu mu gutuma ibikoresho vyo gutumatumanako bitizewe bitemererwa gukorera mu gihugu cacu
 "Izi ngingo nshasha ni nkenerwa mu bikorwa vyacu bibandanya vyo gukingira Abanyamerika icoza gihungabanya umutekano wabo biciye mw’itumatumanako”
 Kubera iyi ngingo itaraba ivya kahise, aya makompanyi ari ku rutonde arashobora kubandanya agurisha ibidandazwa vyayo vyari bisanzwe vyemewe kugurishwa muri Amerika
 Ariko FCC ivuga ko iriko irarondera insiguro ku ngingo zizosubirwamwo muri kazoza ku bijanye n’ibikoresho vyari vyaramaze kwemererwa kwinjira canke kugurishwa, ibi bigasigura ko bishoboka y’uko impusha zisanzwe zihari zishobora kuzofutwa muri kazoza
 Izi ngingo ni zo zanyuma ziherutse gufatwa na Amerika ku makompanyi y’Ubushinwa ku makenga y’uko yoba akora nka maneko, ubwoba bukaba bugenda bwiyongera muri ino myaka ya vuba kuri iki kibazo mu bategetsi ba Amerika
 Ku butegetsi bwa Barack Obama, harafashwe ingingo zo kugabanya ibidandazwa vy’amakompanyi y’Ubushinwa vyinjira kw’isoko ya Amerika
 Ku butegetsi bwa Donald Trump zariyongereye, zikaba zibandanya ku butegetsi bw’umukuru w’igihugu wa kino gihe, Joe Biden

"Dusangiye umubabaro namwe", niko Perezida Vladimir Putin  w’Uburusiya yabwiye umurwi w’abagore ba nyina b’abasirikare b’Uburusiya bari mu ntambara  - bamwe muri bo bakaba barishwe – muri Ukraine
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe ryacishijwe mu  binyamakuru vy’Uburusiya, yavuze ati: "Nta kintu na kimwe cosubirira umuhungu wawe”
 Abenshi muri abo bagore bari mu mihari yegereye Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu w’Uburusiya)
 Abanegura ubutegetsi bwiwe bavuga ko abari muri iyo nama bacaguwe mu bwitonzi
 Mu Burusiya, abatavuga rumwe nawe ku gitero yakoze kuri Ukraine bagenda biyongera
 Mu gihugu cose, abagore bafise abana babo bari mu gisirikare baridoga ku mugaragaro ko abahungu babo bariko bararungikwa ku rugamba ata nyigisho zihagije bahawe kandi ata n’ibirwanisho n’imyambaro bikwiye bafise, cane cane mu gihe igihe c’ubukonje burenze urugero cageze
 Bamwe bagiriza igisirikare c’Uburusiya ko abo carungitse ku nguvu cabashize “ku risongoye”, inyuma yo gutsindwa bikomeye ku rugamba mu misi iheze
 Abasirikare bababa 100
000 b’Abarusiya n’abandi bababa 100
000 ba Ukraine baramaze kwicwa canke gukomereka kuva intambara itanguye ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma uno mwaka, nk’uko bivugwa n’intwazangabo nkuru yo mu gisirikare ca Amerika, Mark Milley
 Mu bintu bidahuse biribonekeza, mu kw’icenda Kremlin yavuze ko hari amakosa yakozwe mu gikorwa co kwegeranya abasirikare b’integabizoza
 Mu nama y’ejo ku wa gatanu ku muhana iwe hafi ya Moscou, Putin yerekanywe yicaye ku meza ndende ari kumwe n’umurwi w’abavyeyi 17
 Bamwe muri bo bari bambaye ibitambara vyirabura ku mutwe – ikimenyetso c’ikigandaro
 Putin yavuze ati: "Nshaka ko mumenya ko jewe ubwanje, hamwe n’abategetsi bose b’igihugu, twifatanije umubabaro namwe”
 Yabwiye umugore umwe ko umuhunu wiwe “yashitse ku ntego yiwe”, ati kandi “ntiyapfiriye ubusa”
 Putin avuga ko yari yashatse kubonana n’aba bavyeyi imbona nkubone kugira ngo yiyumvire we nyene iryo bagona ku bijanye n’ingene ibintu bimeze ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Yamenyesheje kandi ko igihe cose yama avugana n’abasirikare b’Uburusiya bari ku rugamba, aho avuga ko ari “intwari”
 Umukuru w’igihugu kandi asaba aba bagore kwima amatwi “amakuru y’ibinyoma” ku vyerekeye intambara ku mboneshakure canke ku mbuga hwaniro
 Mu gihe kuronka amakuru yizewe ku kungene ibintu bimeze muri Ukraine bigoye kubera Kremlin igenzura ibica mu binyamakuru, abantu benshi bahisemwo kuzunguruka iri genzura baciye ku buhinga bwa VPN kugira ngo baronke amakuru
 Mu cegeranyo c’iyi nama casohowe na Kremlin haciye amasaha make, abatari bake muri abo bagore basanze bari mu mihari yegereye Putin
 Aba bagore bava mu turere dutandukanye tw’Uburusiya, nk’uko iki cegeranyo kibivuga, harimwo n’imiburiburi umwe yavuye mu karere kitangaje ko ari igihugu cigenga kw’izina rya Repubulika  ya Luhansk mu buseruko bwa Ukraine, Moscou iherutse  gutangaza ko yihagiye mu mezi aheze
 Umunywanyi w’umuhari Front populaire panrusse/All-Russia People's Front wegamiye Kremlin, na we nyene niho yari ari, co kimwe n’uwundi wo mu muhari uzwi nka Combat Brotherhood usanzwe wegeranya imfashanyo kugira zihabwe abasirikare b’Abarusiya
 Umushingamateka wo mu mugambwe uri ku butegetsi mu Burusiya, United Russia, na we nyene yari muri iyo nama, nk’uko bivugwa n’ibinyamakuru bimwe bimwe vyegamiye uruhande rw’abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi

