 Urubanza rwashikirijwe n’amashirahamwe adaharanira ivyicaro vya poritike yitwarira reta y’Uburundi ku bijanye n’ikiringo ca gatatu c’umuhisi Perezida Petero Nkurunziza, rwatanguye mu kw’indwi 2015 rukaza kurangira mu kwa cumi na rimwe 2021, ariko rumenyekana mu kw’icenda  2022 haheze imyaka irenga ibiri ico kiringo caraheze, n’uwagitwaye yaramaze gupfa
 Imbere y’urwo hari urundi reta  y’Uburundi yitwariwemwo n’umugambwe Uprona uyagiriza ko yahonyanze amategeko mu kwanka inzego zawo zari zatowe mu 2009,  nk’uko bivugwa na Tatien Sibomana arongoye uruhande rw’uyu mugambwe ruvugwa ko rutavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi
 Sentare ya Afrika y’Ubuseruko yaruciye ku wa 28 Munyonyo (11) 2014,  itegeka reta gutunganiriza uruhande rw’uyo mugambwe rwari rwitwaye rusaba kwubahiriza inzego zawo zari zatowe mu 2009
 Ariko abitwaye bararindiriye ko ruja mu ngiro amaso ahera mu nzira
 Iyi sentare iherutse kandi gutegeka reta y’Urwanda guha umuriyoni w’amadorari umurwizatunga Tribert Rujugiro Ayabatwa, inyuma y’aho isanze reta ya Kigali yarahonyanze amasezerano agenga umuryango w’Ibihugu vya Afrika y’Ubuseruko mu kwihagira no kugurisha inyubakwa yiwe y’ubucuruzi
 Reta y’Urwanda ntiravuga nimba izoshira mu ngiro iki cemezo, ariko umunyamabanga ntayegayezwa mu bushikiranganji bw’ubutungane bw’ico gihugu, Theophile Mbonera, yavuze ko iyi ngingo yafashwe mu mpera z’ukwa munani uno mwaka ibabaje kandi ko reta yari kwihweza uru rubanza kugira ngo irabe ko yokwunguruza, nk’uko vyandikwa n’ikinyamakuru The East African
 Reta y’Uburundi kandi iherutse gutsindwa mu rubanza rwo ku wa 30 Nyakanga (9) rwashingishijwe n’umuryango wa Evariste Sebatutsi kw’itongo riri ahitwa Kizingwe mu gisagara ca Bujumbura
 Urwo rubanza rwari rumaze imyaka 20
 Umuryango wa Sebatutsi uvuga ko utaratunganirizwa kubera reta y’Uburundi yunguruje urubanza
 Ikibazo kihari ni ukumenya nimba iyi sentare ifise ububasha bwo gutera igitsure amareta y’ibihugu kugira ngo ashire mu ngiro ivyemezo biba vyafashwe n‘iyi sentare
 Abahinga baremeranya ko kugira ngo imanza ziciwe na sentare nk’iyi, co kimwe n’izindi sentare mpuzamakungu, zishirwe mu ngiro, ari ngombwa ko reta y’igihugu kanaka iba ifise ugushaka
 Christian Garuka Nsabimana umuhinga mu mategeko mpuzamakungu, avuga ko hari izo ama reta ashira mu mu mgiro ariko ntibimenye benshi kuko atari  ngombwa ko ibitangaza
 Ati: “Rimwe na rimwe n’iyo igihugu gishize mu ngiro icemezo ca sentare, hari igihe abantu batabimenya kuko si ngombwa ko babitangaza mu binyamakuru


rero hari igihe babishira mu ngiro abantu ntibabimenye, nk’uko hari igihe bashobora kubishira mu ngiro abantu bakabimenya
 “Ntitwokwihutira kuvuga ko buri gihe batazishira mu ngiro”
 Hagati aho, Nsabimana abona ko imwe mu ngorane y’iyi sentare ari uko idafise inguvu zo gutuma ivyemezo yafashe bishirwa mu ngiro
 Ati: “Iyo bamaze [abacamanaza] gufata icemezo, ni ngombwa ko tumenya ko iyi sentare idafise igipolisi kizogenda gushira mu bikorwa icemezo yafashe
 “Kugira ngo kije mu bikorwa, hoba ico twokwita ubushake bwa poritike
 Buri gihugu nico gifise inshingano zo gushira mu bikorwa ivyavuye muri urwo rubanza”
 Asigura ko abacamanza b’iyi sentare bafise ububasha bwo gutegeka igihugu ariko ko badafise ububasha bwo gutuma ingingo bafashe ishirwa mu bikorwa
 Agereranya n’amasentare yo hagati mu gihugu, Nsabimana avuga ati: “Nico kimwe no mu gihugu hagati, iyo nk’akarorero uburanye na reta uyagiriza ko yakunyaze, hanyuma sentare igategeka ko reta iguha indishi y’akababaro
 Iyo reta idafise ugushaka kwa poritike, sentare ntishobora kuja mu bigega vya reta muri banki y’igihugu ngo ivanemwo ayo mafaranga hanyuma iyaguhe
 “Sentare iyo ifashe ingingo yoyo iba ikoze akazi kayo ku kibazo gishikirijwe iyo sentare”
 Umuntu yokwibaza akamaro k’imanza zicibwa n’iyi sentare mu gihe bishobora gushika ugasanga urubanza rugiye gucibwa rwaramaze guta igihe
 Akarorero ni urubanza rujanye n’ikiringo ca gatatu c’uwari umukuru w’Uburundi, umuhisi Pereto Nkurunziza
 Iyi sentare yagiye kwemeza ko ico kiringo cari giteye kubiri n’amategeko muri Munyonyo 2021,  ariko urwaciwe ntirwigeze ruja ahabona gushika muri Nyakanga (9) 2022
 Yaba reta y’Uburundi, yaba sentare yo nyene ubwayo, bose babona ko ingingo yafashwe ataco ishobora kumara kubera ico kiringo camaze kurangira, kandi  n’uwo cega nawe akaba atakiriho
 Asigura igituma izo manza ziteba gucibwa, umuhinga Christian Garuka Nsabimana abona ko imvo nyamukuru ari uko iyo sentare idafise uburyo bukwiye, bigatuma abacamanza bose badashobora kuba i Arusha igihe cose
 Ati: “Ingorane z’iyi sentare, abacamanza bayo bose ntabwo baba i Arusha, hariyo babiri gusa
 Abandi bajayo nka rimwe canke kabiri mu mwaka
 “Kumbure gishobora kuba ari ikibazo c’uburyo, kuko iyo sentare, nk’uko twagiye tubisoma, buri gihe ivuga ko, iyaba vyakunda ko ibihugu bishiramwo amafaranga ahagije, vyari gutuma abo bacamanza uko ari batanu baguma bakora akazi kabo umwanya wose nk’abacamanza, ariko siko bimeze”
 Ku bwiwe, ikosa si abacamanza, “ni ikosa ry’ibihugu bigize umuryango wa Afrika y’Ubuseruko bidashiramwo amafaranga ahagije, ibi bigatuma abacamanza badashobora kuguma i Arusha”
 Abari ku ruhande rwitwariye reta bakayitsinda ariko ntirushire mu ngiro, bobo bagumana icizere ko bitebe bitebuke hazogera igihe urubanza rugashirwa mu ngiro
 Kubwa Tatien Sibomana imanza z’amasentare mpuzamakungu zirakunda kugira ingorane z’ikurikizwa kubera “abategerezwa kuzikurikiza ni ayo mareta nyene kenshi ari nayo aba yatsinzwe”
 Avuga ko “ayo masentare aba yashizweho n’abo bakuru b’ibihugu nyene” adafise inguvu zo kugondoza abo bakuru b’ibihugu ngo bakurikize imanza ziba zaciwe
 Ati: “Abategetsi [batsinzwe]  bakiri ku ngoma biragoye ko [urubanza] rukurikizwa, ariko urubanza ntiruhera kuko rumaze gusomwa, rurashobora guteba gukurikizwa mugabo impera n’imperuka ruzokurikizwa”
 "Uurubanza rwaciwe reta kanaka igatsindwa, n’inyuma y'imyaka mirongo haje reta yindi, izovyishuzwa, isabwe gukurikiza urwo rubanza"
 Tatien Sibomana abona kandi ko biba "bivana n’ababa barongoye ayo masentare kuko ahandi barafise ububasha bwo kugondoza igihugu kanaka gukurikiza urwo rubanza"
 Ati: "Na cane cane barashobora guhana ico gihugu, bakagifatira ibihano muri uwo muryango, canke bakagica n’amande n’ibindi bihano, mugabo ivyo vyose biravana n’ugushaka kwa poritike"
 "Rero iyo miryango irabaho mugabo ugasanga iyo itarongowe n’abantu bafise intumbero y’uko ivyo basezeranye bikurikizwa mu mategeko agenga ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu canke mpuzakarere, canke ivyemezo vy'ayo masentare baba bashinze, biraheza bikagorana"
 Nsabimana wewe avuga ko iyo iyi sentare imaze gufata icemezo iba ihejeje, ko haba hasigaye igikorwa c’uburongozi bwo muri ico gihugu, aho bushobora kuvuga buti: “Twaratsinzwe urubanza, dufise inshingano zo kurushira mu ngiro”
 “Igihe batabishize mu ngiro nta kundi bishobora kugenda”
 Christian Garuka Nsabimana  avuga ko mu masezerano y’Umuryango wa Afrika y’Ubuseruko ata hantu na hamwe higeze hategekanywa ko igihugu kitubahiriza ivyemezo vya Sentare ya Afrika y’Ubuseruko bayifatira ibihano, uretse ko gusa kiboneka nk'ikigaba
 Ati: “Nta nkurikizi uretse ko ico gihugu gica cigaragaza mu rwego rw’Umuryango ko ari igihugu kidakurikiza ivyemezo vya sentare”
 Nsabimana asigura ko igikorwa nyamukuru c’iyi sentare ari ukuraba ko ibihugu bihurikiye mu muryango wa Afrika y’Ubuseruko bikurikiza amategeko vyishiriyeho agenga uyu murango
 Ati: “Akamaro sentare iragafise kuko itahari, fata ko ibihugu vyishize hamwe kugira ngo bishireho EAC, mu gihe iyo sentare yoba itariho, buri gihugu coza cifatira inzira uko kivyumva
 “Niyo mpamvu sentare ihari kugira ngo ifashe ibihugu gusesengura ingendo yavyo, amategeko batora imbere mu gihugu, niba kandi vyubahiriza ibitegekanijwe muri ayo masezerano ashiraho EAC”
 Asigura ko akamaro kanini ni uguhagararira amasezerano ashiraho umuryango wa Afrika y’Ubuseruko, igakurikirana igihugu kitariko kirayashira mu ngiro

U﻿mwanditsi E Jean Carroll yitwariye Donald Trump mu ntara ya New York amwagiriza kuba yaramufashe ku nguvu mu myaka ya 1990
 C﻿arroll w'imyaka 78 abaye mu bambere bituye ubutungane nk'uko bitegekanijwe mw'itegeko riha ubwo burenganzira abakorewe ico caha bakuze, ryagiye mu bikorwa ku musi wa kane
 I﻿ryo tegeko ry'iyo ntara riha ikiringo c'umwaka abakorewe icaha kugira biture ubutungane ku caha co gufatwa ku nguvu i New York,  mu gihe ikiringo co kwitwara kiba cararenze ufatiye ku mategeko
 U﻿wo yahoze ari umukuru w'igihugu yarahakanye ivyo yagirizwa
 C﻿arroll avuga ko yafatiwe ku nguvu mu cumba bahinduriramwo impuzu mu mangazini y'abakire iri New York haraheze imyaka 27
 I﻿tegeko rigenga abafashwe ku nguvu bakuze rirekurira abakorewe icaha kubimenyesha, mu gihe babikorewe barenza imyaka 18 kandi bikaba kw'itariki ya kera irenze ku gihe gitegekanijwe gukurikiranwa ugereranije n'ibindi vyaha
 I﻿ryo tegeko ryisunze iriheruka gushingwa ryerekeye ihohoterwa rikorerwa abana, rigenga abakorewe icaha, bagahohoterwa bakiri bato
 I﻿tegeko rihana abahohoteye abana, ryatanguye kuja mu bikorwa mu 2019, ryatanze ikiringo c'imyaka ibiri kugira abakorewe ico caha babivuge
 Imanza zoba zishika 11
000 zarashinzwe i New York aho bitwariye amashengero, ibitaro hamwe n'ibindi bigo hisunzwe iryo tegeko
 C﻿arroll kandi yitwariye prezida Trump ko yamwagirije ububeshi igihe ubwa mbere yavuga ivyo yamukoreye ku mugaragaro mu 2019
 Trump yavuze ko ivyo Carroll amwagiriza ari "ibihimbano"
 B﻿itegekanijwe ko urwo rubanza ruzoba itariki 6 z'ukwezi kwa kabiri
 M﻿w'itangazo, umushingwamanza wa Carroll, Roberta Kaplan, yavuze ko urubanza rushasha rwashinzwe ku musi wa kane rutumbereye kubaza Trump icaha co gufata ku nguvu yoba yarakoze
 A﻿lina Habba, aburanira Trump, yabwiye ibimenyeshamakuru ko, n'aho yubaha akanatangarira abantu bavuga ivyabashikiye "uru rubanza ruciye kubiri n'intumbero y'iryo tegeko" kandi "rushobora gutuma ivyo abakorewe icaha nyabo bavuga bidahabwa agaciro"
 H﻿ari n'abandi bategura kwitura sentare bishimikije iryo tegeko rishasha
 A﻿ha harimwo kwitwarira mu kivunga Robert Hadden, yahoze ari umuganga w'abagore ku bitaro vyakorana na New York-Presbyterian hamwe na kaminuza ya Columbia, yagirijwe n'abagwayi barenga mirongo ibiri ko yabafashe ku nguvu
 Mu 2016, H﻿adden yarahamwe n'ivyaha bifatiye ku gufata ku nguvu muri sentare y'intara, ariko ahakana ivyaha yagirizwa n'igihugu cose vyo gukubagura abagore bagwaye mu myaka irenga mirongo ibiri
 A﻿bashingwamanza b'abafashwe ku nguvu bibaza ko iryo tegeko rihaye akaryo abantu, batari bashoboye kubikora imbere, kubera gutinya kugirirwa nabi canke imvune vyabasizemwo, kwigaragaza
 A﻿yandi mareta menshi yarongereje ikiringo canke arafuta vy'agateganyo amategeko y'ikiringo ivyaha vyo gufata ku nguvu bimara kugira bihanwe, bivuye kw'isekeza rya #MeToo mu 2018, nka New Jersey, Californie, Arizona na Montana

Umuhari w’inyeshamba utegerezwa guhagarika intambara wongere uve mu turere wigaruriye, iyo ni imwe mu ngingo zikomeye zafashwe n’abakuru b’ibihugu bari bakoraniye mu nama ejo ku wa gatatu i Luanda muri Angola
 Barerekanye impungenge ku kungene M23 ibandanya ironka ibirwanisho bihanitse n’ubundi buryo buyituma ikora ibitero ku ngabo za Congo, hamwe n’uko imirwi yitwaje ibirwanisho ibandanya ikiyogoza mu buseruko bwa Congo “bikaba bibangamiye amahoro n’umutekano mu karere kose”
 Haraciye amezi intambara ari urutavanako mu buseruko bwa Congo hagati y'ingabo za reta, FARDC n'umuhari M23, ukaba umaze kwigarurira uturere tutari duke dukikuje umugwa mukuru w'intara ya Kivu ya Ruguru, Goma
 Muri iyo nama, aba bategetsi b’ibihugu vy’akarere bemeje ko mu gihe M23 itokurikiza ivyo bayitegeka bazoca basaba ingabo z’akarere ko zikoresha inguvu
 B﻿BC yagerageje kuvugisha abavugizi ba M23 kuri iyi myanzuro ya Luanda, ariko ntibirashoboka gushika ubu
 Uyu muhari w’inyeshamba wagirizwa ko ushigikiwe n’Urwanda ariko ukabihakana, co kimwe nyene na reta y’Urwanda
 Ibiro bishinzwe Africa mu bunyamabanga bw’imigenderanire bwa Amerika bimenyesha ko bishyigikiye inama ya Luanda, kandi ko kugira ngo amahoro agaruke mu buseruko bwa Congo, bisaba ko : “M23 ihagarika intambara, Urwanda ruhagarika gufasha M23, impande zose zikareka amajambo y’urwanko zikubahiriza ivyo ziyemeje ku mahoro n’ugusubiza hamwe”
 Kuri uyu wa 23 Munyonyo (11),  Perezida João Manuel Lourenço wa Angola yahamagaje abakuru b’ibihugu vy’akarere kugira ngo bige ikirangamisi c’ibikorwa vyihuta mu ntumbero yo guhagarika intambara no kuva mu turere M23 yigaruriye idatevye, be no kwiga  ingene umugambi w’amahoro wa Nairobi na Luanda woshirwa mu ngiro
 Abakuru b’ibihugu bitavye iyo nama, aribo Perezida Evariste Ndayishimiye w’Uburundi akaba n’umukuru w’Umuryango wa Afrika y’Ubuseruko, Felix Tshisekedi wa Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo, umushikiranganji Vincent Biruta yaserukiye Perezida Paul Kagame w’Urwanda, hamwe na Uhuru Kenyatta yagenywe n’Umuryango wa Afrika y’Ubuseruko (EAC) kugira ngo ahagararire ibiganiro vya Nairobi, bibanze ku kungene umutekano uhagaze mu buseruko bwa Congo, aho babonye ko ibintu bitameze neza
 Zimwe mu ngingo zafashwe mu ntumbero yo guhagarika intambara muri ako karere, harimwo ko umuhari M23 utegerezwa guhagarika ibitero ku ngabo za Congo na MONUSCO kuva isaha cumi na zibiri z’umugoroba zo ku wa 25 Munyonyo (11), ni ukuvuga ejo ku wa gatanu
 M23 itegekwa gukurikiza ata guhigimanga ivyashitsweko n’abakuru b’ibihugu ba EAC i Nairobi na Luanda, be n’abakuru ba gisirikare b’ibihugu vya EAC mu nama yabo yabereye i Bujumbura ku wa 08 Munyonyo
 Bemeje kandi ko uyu muhari utegekwa gusubira ku birindiro vyawo vy’imbere y’intambara
 “Mu gihe M23 wogambarara ntuve mu turere twose ugenzura muri kino gihe, abakuru b’ibihugu ba EAC bazoca bategeka ingabo z’akarere gukoresha inguvu kugira ngo zishikane”, niko itangazo baraye basohoye rivuga
 Amasezerano ya Nairobi ategekanya ko ingabo za Kenya zizorungikwa mu gisagara ca Goma, be no mu turere twa Bunagana, Rutshuru na Kiwanja twigaruriwe na M23
 Aba bakuru b’ibihugu bemeje kandi ko kizira gusubira gufasha umuhari M23 n’iyindi mihari yose y’inyeshamba yaba iyo muri Congo canke mvamahanga, haba mu buryo bwa gisirikare canke bwa poritike
 Bategeka imihari FDLR-FOCA, RED-TABARA, ADF n’iyindi mirwi yitwaje ibirwanisho ikorera ku butaka bwa Congo gushira ibirwanisho hasi idatevye kandi igasubira mu bihugu vyayo ataco irinze gusaba, nk’uko biri mu masezerano ya Nairobi
 Basaba kandi ko hoba ibiganiro hagati ya Congo n’Urwanda mu ntumbero yo kunagura imigenderanire hagati yavyo
 U﻿munsi wo ku wa gatanu itariki 25 ukwezi kwa 11 wafashwe nk'umunsi-fatiro (Jour J canke Umunsi J)
 U﻿retse ko ariwo munsi umugwi M23 wategetswe ko ariho uzohagarikirako intanbara kuva isaha 12 z'umugoroba, n'ikirangaminsi c'ingene izindi ngingo zizohsiurwa mu ngiro zifatira kuri uwo munsi

Igipolisi co mu Buhindi cagiriza imbeba ko zononye hafi ibiro 200 vy’urumogi rwafashwe ruriko ruracuruzwa rukabikwa mu birindiro vy’igipolisi
 Sentare yo mu karere ka Uttar Pradesh ivuga iti: "Imbeba ni ibikoko bito cane kandi bidatinya abapolisi
 Biragoye kuzinyegeza uru rumogi”
 Sentare yasavye abapolisi gushira ahabona iri banga nk’icemezo mu manza zerekeye urucuruzwa rw’ibiyayuramutwe
 Umucamanza yashize ahabona imanza zitatu aho urumogi rwariwe n’imbeba
 Umucamanza Sanjay Chaudhary avuga ko igihe sentare isabiye abapolisi kuzana uru rumogi rwafashwe kugira rube icemezo, yabwiwe ko ibiro 195 vy’urumogi “vyononywe” n’imbeba
 Mu rundi rubanza rwerekeye ibiro 386 vy’ico kiyayuramutwe, igipolisi catanze icegeranyo kivuga ko “igice kimwe” c’uru rumogi “cariwe n’imbeba”
 Umucamanza Chaudhary avuga ko hari ibiro 700 vy’urumogi rwafashwe rukabikwa ku birindiro vy’igipolisi mu karere ka Mathura kandi ko “rwose rushobora guterwa n’imbeba”
 Avugako abapolisi badafise ubuhinga bwo gutorera umuti iki kibazo kubera imbeba ari “ibikoko bito cane”
 Avuga ko inzira yonyene yo gukiza ibi bidandazwa vyafashwe kugira ngo “izi mbeba zidatinya” ntizivyonone, ari uko bigurishwa ica munara mu mazu y’ubushakashatsi be n’amakompanyi ahingura imiti, hanyuma inyungu zikaja mu kigega ca reta
 Umushingamateka Singh, umukuru w’igipolisi mu karere ka Mathura, yabwiye abanyamakuru ko urumogi hafi rwose rwabitswe mu birindiro vy’igipolisi biri hafi yiwe “rwononekaye kubera imvura nyinshi”, ko atari imbeba zarwononye
 Mu 2018 abapolisi umunani ba Argentina barirukanywe mu kazi inyuma yo kwagiriza imbeba ko ari zo zatumye inusu y’itoni y’urumogi rwari rwabitswe mu bigega vy’igipolisi rubura
 Ariko abahinga bamirira kure ibi bivugwa, bakavuga ko ibi bikoko bito bititiranije uru rumogi n’indya, kandi ko “iyo hagira imbeba nyinshi zihereza uru rumogi, nyinshi zari gutorwa mu bubiko zapfuye”
 Mu 2017, igipolisi mu karere ka Bihar kari mu buseruko caragarije imbeba ko zanyoye amalitiro ibihumbi y’inzoga yafashwe umwaka umwe inyuma y’aho reta ifatiye itegeko ribuza kugurisha no kunywa inzoga
 Mu 2018, abafundi bari bagiye gukora imashini y’amafaranga yari yononekaye  mu karere ka Assam basanze inoti zifise agaciro k’imiriyoni 1,2 (ni ukuvuga ibihumbi 14,6 vy’amadorari y’abanyamerika)  z’amarupiya zari zatabaguritse, bakavuga ko zari zononywe n’imbeba

Mu gisagara cose ca Lviv kiri mu burengero bwa Ukraine nta muyagankuba ukiharangwa inyuma yo kuvugwa ko habaye ibitero hirya no hino mu gihugu - harimwo n'umugwa mukuru Kyiv
 I﻿gihugu kibanyi ca Moldavie na co nyene kivugwamwo ibura ry'umuyagankuba "hose", n'aho kitatewe co ubwaco
 Umukuru w'igisagara ca L﻿viv yasavye abantu kwinyegeza, mu gihe uwurongoye akarere ka Kyiv kose  avuga ko inyubakwa za nkenerwa n'amazu yo kubamwo vyatewe
 U﻿burusiya buherutse kwongereza ibitero vyabwo ku bibanza bitanga umuyagankuba muri Ukraine
 Icegera c'umushikiranganji wa mbere Andrei Spinu akaba yanditse kuri Twitter ati:"I﻿gice kirenga ca Moldavie ntikigira amatara
" Yagize ati:"Umwijima henshi muri Moldavie inyuma y'ibitero vy'uyu musi vy'Uburusiya ku bibanza bitanga umuyagankuba muri Ukraine
" Imbere y'uko haba ibitero, inzamba zo kugabisha ibitero vyo mu kirere zavuze muri Ukraine hose, zica zikurikirwa n'inkuru zerekeye ibitero vyakozwe mu bibanza bimwe bimwe
 U﻿mukuru w'igisagara ca Lviv, Andriy Sadovy, yavuze ko abana n'abigisha bajanywe mu kibanza co kwikingira - aca asaba abavyeyi kutaza kubatora imbere y'uko inzaba zo kugabisha ibitero zinuma
 G﻿ato imbere yo kumenya ivyabaye i Kyiv na Lviv, abategetsi bavuze ko ubumanuko bwa Ukraine bwasubiye kandi guterwa
 U﻿mukuru w'intara ya Mykolaiv yagabishije "ku rufaya rwa rokete" ruriko rurava mu bumanuko no mu buseruko
 M﻿u karere kahegereye ka Zaporizhzhia, umwana w'uruyoya yishwe igihe misile yagwa ku bitaro vy'abana, nk'uko vyamenyeshejwe n'abajejwe ibikorwa vyo gutabara
 I﻿bitero vyagirijwe Uburusiya ariko nta co buravuga ku bitero vyo kuri uyu wa gatatu
 I﻿bura ry'amatara ritunganijwe canke ritari ku kirangamisi risigaye ari irisanzwe mu turere twinshi twa Ukraine inyuma y'ibi bitero vya vuba
 U﻿turere twinshi twa Ukraine twatewe kuri uyu wa gatatu twegereye ibihugu bibanyi, harimwo Lviv kari ku birometero 50 uvuye muri Pologne, aho igisase gitegera misile zo mu kirere cahitanye abantu babiri mu ndwi iheze
 I﻿bisagara vya Chervonohrad na Yavoriv na vyo vyegereye urubibe Ukraine ihana na Pologne, na ho nta matara aharangwa
 I﻿bitero vy'Uburusiya vyarononye hafi igice c'ibibanza bitanga umuyagankuba muri Ukraine, abantu imiliyoni n'imiliyoni bakaba batagira umuyagankuba mu gihe ibipimo vy'ubushuhe bibandanya bimanuka muri iki gihe c'imbeho
