Abakinyi ba Irani banse kuririmba ururirimbo rw’igihugu imbere y’urukino rwabahuje n’Ubwongereza mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi, mu bisa n’ukwifatanya n’abari mu myiyerekano yiyamiriza reta mu gihugu cabo
 Bamwe mu bafana bavugije induru abandi bazomera mu gihe ururirimbo rw’igihugu rwariko rurasamirana, abandi nabo bafise ivyapa vyanditseko ngo “Umugore, Ubuzima, Ubwigenge”
 Imboneshakure ya Iran yaciye ibikata, ihagarika kwerekana ururirimbo rw’igihugu ruriko ruraririmbwa, maze ica yerekana amashusho arambuye y’ikibuga
 Mu mezi aheze, iyo myiyerekano yaratujijwe bikomeye
 Yavuye ku rupfu rwa Mahsa Amini, umugore w’imyaka 22 yapfiriye mu gasho mu kw’icenda, inyuma yo guhagarikwa n’igipolisi kijejwe inyitafo yagirizwa ko yahonyanze amategeko ruhasha ajanye no kwitwikira
 Abaharanira agateka ka zina muntu bavuga ko abari mu myiyerekano barenga 400 bishwe abandi 16
000 barahagarikwa n’abajejwe umutekano bariko batuza iyo myiyerekano
 Abategetsi ba Iran bavuga ko iyi myiyerekano ari “imigumuko” ikokezwa n’abansi b’igihugu bari mu mahanga
 Abafana ba Irani bumviswe kandi baririmba "Ali Karimi" mu gice ca mbere, bashaka kwibutsa uwahoze ari umukinyi, akaba yari umwe mu bantu banegura cane intwaro ya ki-Islam, akongera kandi akaba n’umwe mu bantu bari bazwi cane mu rugamba rwo kwiyamiriza ubutegetsi
 Abafana kandi bumviswe baririmba "Be-Sharaf", bisigura gusuzugura mu rurimi rw’igiperse
 Iri ni ijambo abari mu myiyerekano bakoresha mu guhangana n’abajejwe umutekano muri Irani
 Abenshi mu barwanya ubutegetsi bwa ki-Islam baranegura umurwi nserukiragihugu w’umupira w’amaguru kubera utashigikiye ku mugaragaro imyiyerekano, no kwemera kubonana na Perezida Ebrahim Raisi  mu ndwi iheze
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije imbere y’urukino, kizigenza w’umurwi wa Irani Ehsan Hajsafi yavuze ko abakinyi “bashigikiye” abamaze gusandaba
 Umumenyereza Carlos Queiroz avuga ko abakinyi biwe bari “bafise uburenganzira bwo kugira imyiyerekano” ku vyerekeye agateka k’abagore mu gihugu cabo mu gihe cose “bidateye kubiri n’amabwirizwa ngenderwako y’igikombe c’isi yose kandi biri mu marangamutima y’urukino”
 Abakinyi ba Irani kandi barapfutse ikimenyetso c’umurwi nserukiragihugu wabo igihe bakina inkino zibiri za kivandimwe mu kw’icenda
 Inyuma y’urukino rwa nijoro ku wa mbere batsinzwe n’Ubwongereza 6 - 2 mw’itsinda B, Queiroz yavuze ko indyane za poritike mu gihugu zagize ingaruka mbi ku murwi wiwe
 Uyu mumenyereza w’umunya-Portugal yavuze ati: "Kuri abo bose baza guhungabanya umurwi n’ibibazo ataho bihuriye n’umupira w’amaguru, nta kibanza bafise kubera aba bahungu bacu, ni abakinyi b’umupira w’amaguru gusa
 "Reka abana bikinire umupira
 Kubera iki nico bishakira
 Bashaka guserukira igihugu, guserukira abanyagihugu, co kimwe n’iyindi mirwi nserukiragihugu iri ng’aha
 No mu yindi mirwi nserukiragihugu yose, iwabo hariyo ibibazo”
 Uyu yahoze ari icegera c’umumenyereza wa Manchester United yongerako ati: "Si vyiza kuza muri rino higanwa ry’igikombe c’isi ugaca ubasaba gukora ivyo batajejwe
 Bashaka gutera iteka n’umunezero abanyagihugu
 "Ntushobora no kwiyumvira ivyo aba bana babayemwo mu buzima bwabo mu misi mike iheze, kubera gusa bashaka kwibera abakinyi b’umupira”
 Avuga kuri ivyo vyari bihejeje kuba inyuma y’igice ca mbere, umunyamakuru wa BBC Gary Lineker ashikiriza amakuru y’inkino, yavuze ati: "Cari ikimenyetso gikomeye, gikomeye cane koko
 "Umupira w’amaguru uriko uragerageza gukoresha inguvu zawo ku neza”

Aho bari mw’ikoraniro ryabahuje mw’izinga rya Djerba muri Tunisia ejo ku wa Mungu, abategetsi b’ibihugu bihurikiye mw’ishirahamwe rikoresha ururimi rw’igifaransa, Francophonie, bavuganye umutekano muke ubandanya wiyongera n’ishavu rirangwa muri iryo shirahamwe ku mugabane wa Afrika
 Ariko icuka kibi cagiye kurenga urugero muri iyo nama ya OIF yonyene ubwayo igihe umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo, Jean-Michel Sama Lukonde, yankiye kwifotoza ahagararanye n'abandi kuko harimwo na Paul Kagame, umukuru w’igihugu c’Urwanda
 Congo yagiriza Urwanda gushigikira umuhari w’inyeshamba M23 wigaruriye uduce tutari duke mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru iri mu buseruko bw’ico gihugu, bituma ibihumbi vy’abanyagihugu bata izabo, bitera n’icuka kibi mu karere
 U﻿ Rwanda ruvuga ko rudafasha umuhari wa M23
 Louise Mushikiwabo, umukuru w’iryo shirahamwe rihurikiyemwo ibihugu 88 yavuze ati: “Ibintu vyose vyerekeye iyi ntambara vyaganiriweko”
 Yizeye kandi ko “iri ari ishirahamwe rishobora gufata mu mugongo rikanahimiriza ibiganiro hagati y’impande zishamiranye”
 Iri shirahamwe ryagirizwa ko ataco “rifasha” mu matora y’ubusuma, ukwihagira ubutegetsi n’ama coups d’Etat arangwa mu bihugu birigize
 Mushikiwabo yabwiye AFP imbere y’inama ati: "Ikibazo tubona mu rwaruka rwo muri Afrika ikoresha ururimi rw’igifaransa ni uguhinyura abanyaporitike”, no gucika intege mu buzima bwa misi yose
 Iri shirahamwe ryashinzwe mu 1970 rifise intumbero yo guteza imbere ururimi rw’igifaransa, gukomeza imigenderanire mu gufashanya mu vy'ubutunzi hamwe no gufasha gutorera umuti amatati mpuzamakungu
 Abategetsi benshi ba Afrika berekanye ko batishimiye ingene uburengero bwihuse gufata ingingo ku ntambara yo muri Ukraine, ariko ko atariko bimeze ku ndyane ziri mu bihugu vyabo
 Perezida Emmanuel Macron w’Ubufaransa ku wa gatandatu yavuze ko iri shirahamwe rikwiye kunagura igikorwa caryo mu vy'imigenderanire, Paris (umugwa mukuru w’Ubufaransa) nayo ikavuga ko igiye kurondera ingene hoba ugukurakuranwa mu kurongora iri shirahamwe kuva mu 2024
 Perezida Macky Sall wa Senegal be n’umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Canada Justin Trudeau bari mu bari bitavye iyo nama y’imisi ibiri
 Trudeau yabwiye abanyamakuru ko Canada "itewe umutima uhagaze n'ingene ibintu bimeze muri iki gihe" muri Tunisia, akizera ko amatora yo mu kw’icumi na kabiri kuza y’inama nshingamateka iboneka ko ifise intege nke azogeza igihugu kuri "demokarasi nzima"
 Ku rundi ruhande, Macron yifatiye mu gahanga Uburusiya, abwagiriza ko bukokeza urwanko ku Bufaransa no kugira agatima “k’ubunyeshamba” mu kurondera gushinga imizi mu bihugu vya Afrika, mu gihe Ubufaransa bwagiye butakaza inguvu za gisirikare n’ikibanza bufise muri ino myaka ya vuba
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije inyuma y’iri koraniro, Macron yasabwe kugira ico avuze ku bamunegura bavuga ko Ubufaransa buriko bukoresha ubucuti bwa poritike n’ubutunzi bufitaniye n’ibihugu bwahoze butwara gikoloni ku nyungu zabwo
 Macron yabwiye imboneshakure TV5 Monde ati: “Abandi barakokeza ibi vyiyumviro, ni umugambi wa poritike
 “Si ndi ikijuju
 Abenshi mu bakokeza, rimwe na rimwe bavugira mu biganiro vyanyu, bararihwa n’Uburusiya
 Turabazi”
 Yongerako ati: “Ibihugu vyinshi bishaka gushinga imizi muri Afrika bibikora kugira bihahaze Ubufaransa, bihahaze ururimi rwabwo, bikabiba ikekwe, ariko hejuru ya vyose bikurikirana inyungu kanaka”
 Ubufaransa, igihugu cahoze gitwara gikoloni ibihugu vyinshi vya Afrika y’Uburengero n’iyo hagati, bufise ubucuti bwa gisirikare bumaze igihe kirekire muri Afrika ikoresha igifaransa
 Bwari busanzwe kandi bufise ingabo zimaze imyaka cumi mu gikorwa co kurwanya iterabwoba
 Ababunegura bavuga ko bwananiwe muri ibi  bikorwa vyabwo vya gisirikare, bakabwagiriza ahubwo kubandanya buteza indyane mu karere
 Buhanganye n’Uburusiya mu kurondera gushinga imizi muri Afrika muri ino myaka ya vuba, aho umurwi w’abacangero wigenga Wagner warungitswe mu bihugu bitari bike, harimwo Centrafrique na Mali
 Vyabaye ngombwa ko Paris iva muri Mali inyuma y’aho igisirikare c’iki gihugu gifatiye ubutegetsi mw’itembagazwa ry’ubutegetsi ryo mu 2020, mu gihe imigenderanire itari yifashe neza
 Inyuma y’aho, aba bategetsi ba gisirikare baciye batumako Wagner kugira ngo ibafashe mu ntambara yo kurwanya inyeshamba ziyitirira idini rya Islam imaze imyaka cumi, baca bahagarika imigenderanire n’Ubufaransa
 Uburusiya buvuga ko Wagner idaserukira igihugu kandi ko butayihemba
 Ariko Ubumwe bwa Bulaya bwafatiye ibihano Wagner, buvuga ko ari ikompanyi ikorera mu kinyegero kw’izina rya reta y’Uburusiya
 Mu mwaka uheze, icegeranyo c’ishirahamwe ONU cavuze ko abigisha ba gisirikare b’Abarusiya hamwe n’abasirikare ba Centrafrique bateye abasivire bakoresheje inguvu zirenze urugero, bica mu rudavagi, biragurira amashure baranasahura
 Kremlin yavuze ko cari ikinyoma ko abigisha b'Abarusiya bagize uruhara mu bwicanyi  canke ubusuma muri ico gihugu gituwemwo n’imiriyoni 4
7 z’abantu, kikaba gitunze ubutare bw’inzahabu na diamand

Turukiya yatanguye ibitero vy’indege ku bigo vy’Abakurde muri Iraq na Syria, indwi imwe inyuma y’igitero ca bombe muri Istanbul cagirizwa inyeshamba z’Abakurde
 Ibi bitero – vyiswe Operation Claw-Sword – vyakozwe ku birindiro vy’Abakurde vyakoreshwa mu gutegura ibitero kuri Turukiya, nk’uko bivugwa n’ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi
 Umuvugizi w’Abakurde bakomoka muri Syria avuga ko ibigwati bibiri bibamwo abataye izabo ari vyo vyatewe
 Umuhari PKK wabujijwe ibikorwa uvuga ko atari wo wakoze igitero ca Istanbul
 Igihe ibi bitero vy’indege bitangura, ubushikiranganji bwa Turukiya bujejwe kwivuna abansi bwanditse kuri Twitter ko “isaha yo kwirimbura” yari yageze, bushirako n’isanamu y’indege y’intambara igurutse hamwe n’amashusho y’igisasu gituritse
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi wa Turukiya, Hulusi Akar, yagize ati: "Ubwihisho, ibinogo, amasenga, imyobo n’ububiko vy’abakora iterabwoba vyasambuwe”
 Mu nyuma ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bwa Turukiya bwahavuye buvuga ko ibi bitero ku birindiro vy’inyeshamba z’Abakurde mu buraruko bwa Syria no mu buraruko bwa Iraq vyasambuye ibibanza 89
 Ingabo zirongowe n’Abakurde muri Syria ziyemeje ko zitegerezwa kwihora, zikavuga kandi ko  igisagara ca Kobane catewe hamwe n’ibindi bigwati bibiri bibamwo abantu benshi
 Mu masaha yitereye y’ejo ku wa Mungu, igisasu ca muzinga carasiwe muri Syria kivugwa ko cakomerekeje abantu batatu ku rubibe na Turukiya, nk’uko bivugwa n’ibinyamakuru vyegamiye reta ya Turukiya
 Mu buraruko bwa Syria honyene, abantu 31 barishwe, nk’uko bivugwa n’ishirahamwe rya Syria riharanira agateka ka zina muntu, Syrian Observatory for Human Rights, rifise icicaro mu Bwongereza
 Ntibiramenyekana ibibanza vyatewe muri Iraq
 Ibi bitero bije indwi imwe inyuma y’igitero ca bombe cakozwe kuri rimwe mu mabarabara akoreshwa cane muri Istanbul kigahitana abantu batandatu congera gikomeretsa abarenga 80
 Abategetsi ba Turukiya bagiriza umuhari w’inyeshamba z’Abakurde, PKK, umuhari Turukiya, Ubumwe bwa Bulaya, na Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bifata ko ari uw’iterabwoba, ko ari wo wakoze iki gitero
 Ariko, PKK yoyo ivuga ko idashobora “gutera ibibanza vy’abasivire”, ugahakana ko ata ruhara ubifisemwo
 Abategetsi bahagaritse abantu batari bake bagirizwa ko bafitaniye isano n’iki gitero harimwo umugore w’umunya-Syria bavuga ko ari we yateze iki kibombe
 Imbere yo kumuhagarika, umushikiranganji wa Turukiya ajejwe ubutungane yavuze ko agasaho katuritse hafi y’intebe yari yicayeko umugore  mu kiringo c’iminota 40
 Abantu batanu kandi barengukishijwe muri Bulgaria kuri iki gitero, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP
 Inyeshamba z’Abakurde zimaze imyaka mirongo zirwana zirondera ubutegetsi bwigenga bw’Abakurde mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Turukiya
 Mu myaka mike iheze, Turukiya yarakoze ibitero bitari bike hakurya y’urubibe itera imirwi y’Abakurde ifise ivyicaro mu buraruko bwa Iraq na Syria, mu ntumbero yo kuzibira ibitero ku butaka bwa Turukiya

Umukuru wa Kenya William Ruto uyu munsi yakoze urugendo i Kinshasa, umurwa mukuru w’ico gihugu
 Prezida Ruto yabonanye kandi avugana na mugenziwe wa Congo Felix Tshisekedi
 Uwo mubonano wabo wabaye mu gihe hasibijwe ibiganiro vyari bitegekanijwe gutangura uyu munsi muri Kenya hagati ya reta ya Congo n’imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho mu ntumbero yo kurondera amahoro mu buseruko bwa Congo
 Ico gice c’igihugu kirangwamwo imigwi myinshi yitwaje ibigwanisho na cane cane uwa M23 umaze igihe warasubiye kugwana uranafata ibice bitari bike vy’akarere ka Rutshuru mu ntara ya Nord Kivu
 Mu kiganiro bahaye abamenyeshamakuru bahejeje kubonana, abakuru ba Kenya na Congo bavuze ko ikibazo c’ingene amahoro yogaruka mu buseruko bwa Congo arico nyamukuru baganiriyeko
 Ahagararanye na prezida Willian Ruto wa Kenya, Prezida wa Congo Felix Tshisekedi yasubiyemwo ivyo yari maze kuvuga ko igihugu ciwe cagabweko igitero n’igihugu kibanyi c’u Rwanda
 Tshisekedi yashimiye Ruto ko kuva ashitse ku butegetesi mu kwezi kw’icenda guheze yerekanye ishaka ryo gufasha ico gihugu kugarukana amahoro
 Yagize ati: “Nashaka kumushimira ku gushigikira igihugu cacu
 Kuva ashiste ku butegetsi bw’igihugu ciwe, Prezida wa Kenya Ruto yarerekanye ko afise ishaka rikomeye ryo gufasha igihugu cacu gusubira mu nzira y’amahoro
 Amahoro tumaze imyaka mirongo ibiri turiko turarondera”
 Kenya iri mu bihugu vy’ishirahanjwe rya Afrika y’ubuseruko EAC vyarungitse ingabo gufasha muri ico gikorwa
 Ariko hakomeje kubazwa ibibazo vy’ico izo ngabo zizokora na cane cane ko zizoja mu bikorwa vyo kurwanya imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho nka M23
 N’uyu munsi Willian Ruto yongeye kukibazwa
 Ariko n’ubu ico kugwana bisa n’uko ata nyishu caronse
 Bwana Ruto yagize ati: "Dufise ingabo nyinshi zo gucungera amahoro muri Congo
 Ariko tubiravye nk’umuryango w’akarere, ntitubona ko ayo mahoro yo gucungera ahari
 "Nico gituma hakenewe cane ko haba inteko zo kwubahiriza amahoro biciye mu ngabo za Afrika y’Ubuseruko
 "Inshingano z’izo ngabo z’akarere nizo inteko za Kenya zisunga mu butumwa zagiyemwo muri Congo”
 Uretse Kurungika ingabo, uwahoze ari unukuru w’ico gihugu Uhuru Kenyatta yahawe ubutumwa n’umuryango w’ibihugu vya Afrika y’ubuseruko EAC bwo gufasha kugira habe ibiganiro hagati ya reta ya Congo n’imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho irangwa mu buseruko bwa Congo
 Ibiganiro vyari bitegekanijwe gutangura kuri uyu wa mbere i Nairobi muri Kenya, ariko vyasivye ku munota wa nyuma
 Umuntu akora mw’itegurwa ry‘ivyo biganiro atashimye kumenyekana izina yabwiye BBC ko mu gihe vyose vyasa n’ivyatunganye ngo ibiganiro bibe, batangajwe n’ingene reta ya Congo isa n’iyerekanye ko ata gushaka kugaragara kwo kubizamwo
 Reta ya Congo yavuze ko itazokwemera kuganira n‘umuhari M3, uwo mugwi utavuye mu turere uherutse kwigarurira ukanashira ibigwanisho hasi, ivyo uwo muhari wavuze ko utazokora
 Mu kiganiro abategetsi ba Kenya na Congo bahaye abamenyeshamakuru bahejeje kubonana, ntaco bavuze ku co boba bavuganye ku casibije ibiganiro n’isango rishasha vyoba vyimuriweko

Nyamugigima mw’izinga rikuru rya Indoneziya ari ryo Java yahitanye abantu 162 abandi amajana barakomereka, nk’uko vyatangajwe n’umukuru w’intara Ridwan Kamil
 Iyo nyamugigima y’ubukomezi bwa 5,6 yatanguriye mu muji wa Cianjur uri muri Java y’uburengero, ku burebure bwa 10km uja i kuzimu, nk’uko bivugwa n’ikigo US Geological Survey kigenzura za nyamugigima
 Abantu benshi bajanywe ku bitaro, abandi bavurirwa aho bakomerekeye
 Abajejwe gutabara biteguriye gukora ijoro ryose ngo bagerageze kurokora abandi baheze mu bihomoka vy’amazu
 Agace iyo nyamugigima yashikiyemwo karatuwe cane kandi kakaba kari ku magenge yo gushikirwa n’ugusiduka kw’imisozi, amazu yaho akaba adakomeye – imwe mu mamvu zatumye menshi acika ivu
 Hari amakuru ahushanye ku bijanye n’igitigiri nyaco c’abahasize ubuzima, kandi biragoye kumenya igitigiri nyaco kuko kurondera biracabandanya co kimwe n’utwigoro two gutabara aboba bagihema
 Kare ikigo c’igihugu ca Indoneziya kijejwe ibiza, BNPB, cavuze yuko abantu n’imiburiburi 62 bapfuye, hisunzwe ibiharuro biheruka
 Abantu barenga 13
000 bateshejwe izabo nk’uko vyavuzwe n’abajejwe intwaro, nayo ikigo BNPB kivuga yuko abantu 700 bakomeretse
 Abajejwe intwaro kandi bavuze yuko abakomeretse hamwe n’abahasize ubuzima bashobora kwiyongera kuko hakiri “abantu benshi” baheze mu bihomoka

U﻿mukinyi w'imbere w'Ubufaransa ntazoja mu nkino z'igikombe c'isi ca 2022 muri Qatar inyuma yo gukomereka kw'itako ari mu myimenyerezo
 B﻿enzema yatsindiye 'Ballon d'Or' ya 2022, agashimwe gahabwa umukinyi wa mbere kw'isi buri mwaka mu mupira w'amaguru, inyuma yo gufasha umugwi wiwe wa Real Madrid gutwara igikombe c'imigwi yabaye iya mbere iwabo n'ico ihiganwa ryo muri Espagne, La Liga
 U﻿mugwi nserukiragihugu w'Ubufaransa uvuga ko yagize ikibazo kw'itako, ko hari igihe atoshobora kuja muri iryo higanwa
 W﻿ongeyeko uti:"Umugwi wose usangiye umubabaro na Karimi kandi umwipfurije gukira vuba
" I﻿shirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru ry'Ubufaransa rivuga ko ibipimo vyemeje ko yakomeretse kw'itako "bikaba bimusaba kumara indwi zitatu kugira atore mitende"
 U﻿bufaransa buri mu mugwi wa D, bukaba buzokina na Australia itariki 22 z'ukwezi kwa Munyonyo (11), na Danmark itariki 26 z'ukwezi kwa Munyonyo (11) hamwe rero na Tunisia itariki 30 z'uko kwezi nyene
 U﻿mumenyereza mukuru Didier Deschamps afise gushika ku wa mbere ngo abe yatanze izina ry'uwumusubirira, kandi ikikomere ca Benzema w'imyaka 34, amaze gutsindira Ubufaransa ibitego 37 mu nkino 97, n'ikindi gihombo gikomeye kuri uwo mugwi waheruka gutwara ico gikombe c'isi
 B﻿ari basanzwe badafise abakinyi bo hagati Paul Pogba na N'Golo Kante kubera gukomereka, aho ni mu gihe n'umukinyi w'inyuma wa Manchester United Raphael Varane ariko aragerageza kwimenyereza kugira azoshobore gukina inyuma yo kutagaragara mu nkino z'itanu z'umugwi wiwe
 K﻿u musi wa gatatu, umukinyi w'imbere wa RB Leipzig Christopher Nkunku yarakuwe muri mu mugwi w'abazokina muri iryo higanwa inyuma yo gucumbagira bari mu myimenyerezo, aho haciye hahamagarwa umukinyi wa Frankfurt Randal Kolo Muani ngo amusubirire
 U﻿mukinyi w'imbere wa Manchester United Anthony Martial n'umwe mu bashobora guhamagarwa kuza gusubirira Benzema, yari amaze imisi afise ikibazo co mw'itako kuva mu kwezi kwa cumi
 U﻿wo mukinyi wa Real Madrid amaze gukinira uwo mugwi iminota idashika 30  mu nkino zitandatu ziheze
 Y﻿aciye aja gupimwa inyuma y'imyimenyerezo yo ku wa gatandatu - Bwari bubaye ubwa mbere agize imyimenyerezo akayirangiza kuva abagize umugwi uzoja mu nkino z'igikombe c'isi bagiye hamwe bose mu ndwi iheze
 D﻿eschamps yagize ati:"Ndatewe ikigongwe cane na Karim yari yagize intumbero nya mukuru iki gikombe c'isi
 "﻿N'aho ibi bibaye, ndacafitiye icizere umugwi wanje
 Tuzokora uko dushoboye kugira turangize igikorwa kitoroshe kiturindiriye
"
By Shamoon Hafez BBC Sport in Doha, Qatar I﻿nyuma y'imyaka 12 y'ibibazo no kunebagurwa, inkino z'igikombe c'isi mu mupira w'amaguru muri Qatar ziratangura kuri uyu w'Imana
 I﻿myiteguro y'iryo higana rya mbere ribereye mu gihugu c'aba Islam co mu burasirazuba bwo hagati, ntiryavuzwe cane nk'ivyo barivugako
 A﻿riko Fifa yasavye imigwi y'ibihugu 32 izitaba iryo higanwa "gushira inguvu gusa ku rukino", abakiriye iryo higanwa muri Qatar bakaza gutana mu mitwe na Equateur ku kibuga ca Al Bayt (16h00 GMT)
 K﻿u musi ukurikira hazokina Ubwongereza na Iran (13:00) imbere y'uko Reta zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zihura na Wales (19:00)
 Q﻿atar 2022 kizoguma ari kimwe mu bikombe vy'isi vyateye impari n'umwumvikano muke muri kahise k'inkino
 I﻿co gihugu co mu kigobe catsinze ibihugu vya Korea y'Epfo, Ubuyapani, Australia na Amerika vyashaka gutunganya izo nkino, ariko hakaba haravuzwe ko hatanzwe ibiturire kugira Qatar ihabwe ayo mahirwe, ivyo ico gihugu kiguma gihakana
 M﻿u kwezi kwa kabiri 2021, ikinyamakuru The Guardian canditse ko abakozi b'abimukira 6
500 bava mu bihugu vy'Ubuhindi, Nepal, Bangladesh na Sri Lanka bapfiriye muri Qatar kuva ico gihugu gitsindiye gutunganya inkino z'igikombe c'isi
 I﻿vyo biharuro vyegeranijwe hisunzwe ivyo abaserukira ibihugu vyabo muri Qatar
 A﻿riko Qatar ivuga ko ivyo biharuro atari vyo kubera ko abapfuye bose batari abakozi bo mu nyubakwa zo kwitegurira igikombe c'isi
 R﻿eta ivuga ko ibiharuro ifise ari impanuka zahitanye abantu 37 mu bakozi bubaka ibibuga bikokinirwako igikombe c'isi hagati ya 2014 na 2020, batatu gusa akaba ari bo "bazize akazi bakora"
 A﻿riko ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ry'abakozi, International Labour Organisation (ILO) rivuga ko bagabanije ico gitigiri cane
 H﻿ari ubwoba ku bakunzi b'umupira w'amaguru bahuza ibitsina babisangiye ku kungene bazofatwa ufatiye ko ico gihugu kigendera kw'itegeko rya 'Shari', guhiza ibitsina rero mu bisangiye bikaba bitemewe muri ico Qatar
 Amashirahamwe akorana na Fifa mu gutegura iryo higanwa yavuze ko "ibiganiro vyagiye buhoro buhoro" kandi ko " ibintu biteye umutima uhagaze" bikiriho
 K﻿u musi umwe imbere y'uko iryo higanwa ritangura, prezida wa Fifa Gianni Infantino yagirije ibihugu vya Buraya "ubwiyorobetsi" mu vyo bagiye baravuga ku bijanye n'agateka ka zina muntu muri Qatar
 A﻿mezi atatu imbere y'uko iryo higanwa riba, akana ka Fifa karemeye ivyasabwa n'imigwi yo mw'ishirahamwe rya Amerika y'epfo, Conmebol, vyo kwungururiza intango y'iryo higanwa ku musi umwe imbere y'aho ryotanguriye
 H﻿anyuma, imisi ibiri imbere y'uko ihiganwa ritangura, abariteguye bamenyesheje abafana ko badashobora kugura no kunwera inzoga ku bibuga vyose ko ari umunani,  no mu micungararo yavyo
