By Max Matza BBC News, Washington H﻿agenywe umushikirizamanza yigenga wo mu bushikiranganji bw'ubutungane muri Amerika wo guhagarikira amatohoza ku vyaha vy'uwahoze ari prezida Donald Trump
 J﻿ack Smith, yahoze ari umushikirizamanza ku vyaha vyo mu ntambara, yagenywe kuba umuhanuzi adasanzwe w'umushikirizamanza mukuru Merrick Garland mu kiganiro n'abamenyeshamakuru
 A﻿zorongora amatohoza ku kungene Trump yakoresheje inyandiko z'ibanga n'uruhara rwiwe mu gitero co ku nyubakwa y'inama nshingamateka izwi kw'izina rya "Capotol" T﻿rump, asanzwe ariko aragirwako n'ayandi matohoza, arahakana ko yoba yarakoze ikintu gihanwa n'amategeko
 S﻿mith ni we azofata ingingo ubwa nyuma nimba uwo yahoze ari umukuru w'igihugu wo mu mugambwe w'abarepublika, yamaze gutangaza ko azitoza mu kibanza ca prezida mu 2024 mu misi itatu iheze, ategerezwa kuja imbere y'ubutungane
 Ku musi wa gatanu, G﻿arland yavuze ati:"Mu bihe bimwe bimwe bidasanzwe, ni ku neza y'abanyagihugu kugena umushikirizamanza adasanzwe wo guhagarikira amatohoza  n'ikurikiranwa ata ho vyegamiye
 "﻿Kubera ivyabaye muri iyi misi ya vuba, harimwo kuba uwahoze ari prezida yaratangaje ko azitoza mu matora yimirije, n'icipfuzo ca prezida ahari ubu c'uko na we nyene ashobora gusubira kwitoza, naciye mbona ko ari ku neza y'abanyagihugu
" Y﻿avuze ko iyi ngingo izoha icizere abanyagihugu kuri ayo matohoza
 M﻿w'itangazo ryiwe ryo ku musi wa gatanu ari ku muhana iwe i Mar-a-Lago, Trump yariyamirije "ikoreshwa nabi ry'ubutegetsi" ry'ubushikiranganji bw'ubutungane "bwamunzwe na ruswa kandi bukora ku nyungu za politike" mu kugena umushikirizamanza adasanzwe wo mu mugambwe batavuga rumwe
 S﻿mith yahoze ari umushikirizamanza i New York, mu misi ya vuba na ho akaba yahora ari umushikirizamanza mukuru i La Hague aho yakora amatohoza ku vyaha vyo mu ntambara muri Kosovo
 A﻿giye gusubira muri Amerika gutangura akazi kiwe vuba na bwangu nk'uko vyavuzwe na Garland
 Mukwiyama hakiri kare abashobora kuvuga ko afise uruhande yegamiye, ubushikiranganji bw'ubutungane bwavuze ko Smith azwi nk'umuntu ata ho yegamiye muri politike

U﻿wahoze ari prezida wa Kenya, Uhuru Kenyatta hamwe na prezida w'Urwanda Paul Kagame bumvikanye ko hakenewe ihagarikwa ry'intambara mu buseruko ba Republika ya Demokrasi ya Congo n'uko abagwanyi ba M23 bova mu turere baheruka gufata
 K﻿enyatta, umuhuza wa EAC mu matati y'abanye Congo ariko aragerageza guhagarika iyo ntambara - avuye muri Nord Kivu aho umugwi wa M23 wagize ibitero vyinshi muri uyu mwaka, vyatumye abantu bangana barenga ibihumbi 250 bata izabo
 Urwanda ruhakana gushigikira umuhari wa M23 iriko igwanira mu buseruko bwa Congo
 A﻿riko, ufatiye kw'itangazo ry'ibiro vy'umuhuza Kenyatta, prezida w'Urwanda yemeye gufasha umuhuza wa EAC gusaba M23 guhagarika ingwano no kuva mu duce baherutse kwigarurira
 I﻿ryo tangazo ribandanya rivuga ko Kenyatta yavuganiye ku murongo wa telefone na prezida w'Uburundi Evariste Ndayishimiye arongoye ishirahamwe ry'ubuseruko bwa Afrika muri kino gihe, EAC, kw'ishirwa mu bikorwa ry'ivyapfunditse n'abakuru b'ingabo z'ako karere ku ntambara zibera muri Congo harimwo kuja gutuza imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho iri mu buseruko bw'ico gihugu
 N﻿go baravuze kandi kw'itanga ry'imfashanyo ku bamaze guta izabo kubera iyo ntambara ihuza reta na M23
 K﻿enyatta kandi yaravuganye n'umunyamabanga wa Onu, Antonio Guterres kuri ico kibazo c'imfashanyo
 M﻿uri iyi ndwi intambara yarakaze cane, aho igisirikare ca Congo cateye M23 gikoresheje indege n'imodoka zitamenwa
 A﻿ka kamo k'amakungu ko guhagarika intambara kazanye icizere
 V﻿yinshi bizova ku bizova mu biganiro vy'amahoro bitegekanijwe gutangura i Nairobi ku musi wa mbere
 G﻿ushika ubu, ntibiramenyekana nimba umuhari wa M23 uzitaba ivyo biganiro, kuko mu biganiro vya mbere ntiwari watumiwe
 R﻿eta ya Congo yari yamenyesheje ko M23 ari umugwi w'iterabwoba, gutyo ko ukwiye gutuzwa ku nguvu
 I﻿tariki 12 z'uku kwezi, umushikiranganji w'imigenderanire ya Congo n'amakungu yarashize ahabona ibintu bine bisabwa kugira reta yemere kuganira na M23, harimwo kurekura uduce twose yafashe
 C﻿hristophe Lutundula yasubiyemwo ko reta ibona umuhari wa M23 nk'uwo iterabwoba, kandi ko badashobora kuganira na wo ivyo bidahindutse
 R﻿eta ya Congo kandi yagumye yagiriza igihugu c'Urwanda ko ari co gifashe mu mugongo uwo muhari
 I﻿vyo vyose M23 yagumye ibihakana
 Mu ntango z'ukwezi kwa cumi u﻿muhuza w'akarere ko mu buseruko bwa Afrika EAC ku kibazo ca Congo, Uhuru Kenyatta na prezida Evariste Ndayishimiye arongoye iryo shirahamwe bari basavye ko imigwi yose yitwaje ibigwanisho iri muri RD Congo, isubira mu bihugu vyayo
 I﻿vyo biri mw'itangazo abo bategetsi babiri basohoye inyuma y'umubonano wabereye i Bujumbura mu Burundi ku mugwa mukuru w'ubutunzi w'ico gihugu
 I﻿ryo tangazo ryagira riti: "Duhamagariye imigwi yose yitwaje ibigwanisho gusubira mu bihugu yaje ivamwo ata kindi gisabwe
" K﻿enya, Uburundi na Uganda, ni vyo bimaze kurungika ingabo zo kugwanya imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho iri mu buseruko bwa Congo
 I﻿myaka n'imyaka y'intambara yagiye irakongerwa n'inyota yo kugenzura ubutare buri muri aako karere

I﻿tangazo ry'igisirikare c'Urwanda rivuga ko hari isaha indwi z'ijoro aho umusirikare atamenyekanye yoba ari uwa FARDC yajabuka urubibe kuri 'petite barriere' mu karere ka Rubavu aca atangura kurasa ku birindiro vy'abasoda b'Urwanda
 I﻿ryo tangazo ribandanya rivuga ko abasirikare b'Urwanda, RDF bariko barakizura baciye bamurasa baramwica imbere y'uko hagira ico yonona
 K﻿u ruhande rwa DRC nta co baravuga
 B﻿BC Gahuzamiryango yahamagaye Gen Sylvain Ekenge avugira igisirikare ca Congo, avuga ko ata co afise avuga ku vyanditswe n'igisirikare c'Urwanda
 R﻿DF ivuga ko ivyabaye yabimenyesheje umugwi w’abahinga ba gisirikare bo mu karere basanzwe bagenzura bakanatohoza ibibazo vy’umutekano
 I﻿vyo bishitse mu gihe kuri uyu wa gatanu, ibiro vy'umuhuza wa EAC ku ntambara ibire muri Congo, Uhuru Kenyatta, vyasohoye itangazo, aho rivuga ko prezida Paul Kagame w'Urwanda yemeye gutera igitsure umuhari wa M23 ngo uhagarike intambara wongere uve mu duce twose uherutse kwigarurira
 M﻿u gihe vyokwemezwa ko uwo yapfuye yari umusirikare wa RD Congo, ntibuzoba bubaye ubwa mbere umusirikare w'ico gihugu arasirwa kuri urwo rubibe yagirizwa kujabuka kurasa mu Rwanda
 Mu kwezi kwa gatandatu mu 2022, igisirikare c’Urwanda, RDF, caremeje ko hari umusirikare wa Congo yarashwe arapfa inyuma yo kwinjira akarasa kandi agakomeretsa abantu muri Rubavu ku mupaka ivyo bihugu bihana
 Itangazo rya RDF ryavuze ko uwo musirikare wa Congo atamenyekanye umwidondoro,  yari afise inkoho yo mu bwoko bwa AK47 [Kalashinikov]
 Rikavuga ko “Muri iki gitondo hafi y’isaha 08:45 [isaha zibiri n’iminota 45 zo mu gitondo], umusirikare w’umunye-Congo atamenyekanye yari yitwaje inkoho yo mu bwoko bwa AK47 yajabutse “Petite Barriere” ku rubibe rwa Rubavu atangura kurasa abajejwe umutekano b’Urwanda n’abanyagihugu basanzwe bariko barajabuka”
 Bavuga ko  yari yakomerekeje abapolisi babiri b’Urwanda imbere y’uko mugenzi wabo nawe amurasa akamwica
 N;ico gihe iryo tangazo ryavuze ko RDF yaciye yitura umugwi w’abahinga ba gisirikare bo mu karere basanzwe bagenzura bakanatohoza ibibazo vy’umutekano

Ubuyobozi bwa Manchester United buvuga yuko buriko burafata “ingingo zibereye” nyuma y’aho Cristian Ronaldo atangiye ikiganiro akavuga yuko “yagambaniwe n’iyi kipe”
 Uyu musatirizi w’umunye-Portugal yavuze yuko ata “cubahiro” afitiye umumenyereza Erik ten Hag ngo kandi ariko arahindirwa kure ya Old Trafford
 Mu rwandiko handitswe hati “Manchester United muri iki gitondo yafashe ivyemezo bibereye mu gusubiza ku kiganiro Cristiano Ronaldo aheruka guha ibitangazamakuru”
 Iyo kipe nta bindi izorenzako gushika “ivyemezo vyafashwe bishitse ku musozo wavyo”
 Nyuma y’ikiganiro cerekeye ibintu bitandukanye yagiranye n’umunyamakuru Piers Morgna wa TalkTV, kazoza ka Ronaldo muri Man United karacumbagira
 Uwo mugabo w’imyaka 37 azoba ari kapitene wa Portugal mu gikombe c’isi i Qatar, urukino rwabo rwa mbere mu mugwi H rukazobahuza na Ghana ku munsi wa kabiri
 Ntarasubira gukina kubera uburwayi butatangajwe kuva aho abereye kapitene mu rukino United yatsinzwe 3-1 na Aston Villa, itariki 6 Munyonyo (11)
 Ten Hag ntiyashize Ronaldo mw’ikipe mu rukino rw’ihiganwa rya Premier League aho bahura na Chelsea mu kwezi guheze, nyuma y’aho yankiye kwinjira mu kibuga nk’uwusubirira uwundi mu rukino na Tottenham, iminsi itatu imbere yaho
 Aba Red Devils, baheruka gutsinda Fulham 2-1 kuwa Mungu, ni aba gatanu muri Premier League mu mwaka w’inkino wa mbere wa Ten Hag nk’umumenyereza w’iyi kipe

Na Jean Mackenzie U﻿munyamakuru i Seoul Korea ya Ruguru yarashe igisasu cambukiranya imigabane (missile ballistique intercontinental/intercontinental ballistic missile, ICBM), ifise ubushobozi bwo gushika ku butaka bwa Amerika, nk’uko bivugwa n’umushikiranganji w’Ubuyapani ajejwe kwivuna abansi
 Igisata c’Ubuyapani kijejwe gucungera inkengera kivuga ko ico gisasu ca misire gishobora kuba caguye mu nyanja ku birometero vyababa 210 mu burengero bw'izinga Hokkaido
 Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziriyamiriza iraswa ry’iki gisasu, mu gihe Korea y’Epfo yategetse ko hafatwa ingingo ruhasha zo kwihaniza Korea ya Ruguru
 Ejo ku wa kane, umushikiranganji wa Korea ya Ruguru ajejwe imigenderanire Choe Son Hui yaragabishije ko bazokwihora “bikomeye” ku migambi ya Amerika yo kurondera gushinga imizi muri ako karere
 Uwo musi nyene Korea yarekuye igisasu ca misire kiraswa ku ntera ngufi
 Ibi bibaye inyuma y’inama yo ku wa Mungu hagati ya Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika, Yoon Suk-yeol wa Korea y’Epfo hamwe n’umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubuyapani Fumio Kishida aho bari mu nama muri Cambodge
 Umuvugizi w'inama nkuru ya Amerika ijejwe umutekano Adrienne Watson avuga ko Biden yabimenyeshejwe kandi ko Amerika izovugana n'ibihugu bigenzi vyayo
 Umuhanuzi wa Amerika mu vyo umutekano avuga ko “bazokwihora bari hamwe” mu gihe Korea ya Ruguru yoramuka igerageje ikindi kirwanisho ca nikleyeri kigira indwi kimaze kuvugwa amezi atari make n’inzego zijejwe igendereza za Amerika na Korea y’Epfo
 Korea ya Ruguru imaze kurekura ibisasu vya misire birenga 50 mu mezi abiri aheze, vyinshi bikaba ari ibiraswa ku ntera ngufi
 Ibiraswa ku ntera ndende ntibikunze kugeragezwa, kandi bigeramiye Amerika, kubera izo misire zahinguwe ku buryo zigenda zikoreye ibisasu vy’ubumara zikazoshika aho ari ho hose ku butaka bwa Amerika
 Iki gisasu cikekwa ko ari ICBM carashwe isaha zine n’iminota 15 (10:15) mu masaha ya Korea ya Ruguru, ni ukuvuga isaha cumi n’iminota 15 z’ijoro mu masaha y’Uburundi n’Urwanda, hafi y’umugwa mukuru Pyongyang, nk’uko bivugwa n’abakuru ba gisirikare ba Korea y’Epfo
 Cagurutse gushika ku birometero 6
100 uja hejuru, kikaba cageze ku ntera y’ibirometero 1
000, ku muvuduko ungana n’uw’ikindi yarekuye ku wa 22 z’ukwa gatatu, nk’uko bivugwa n’igisirikare ca Korea y’Epfo
 Umushikiranganji w’Ubuyapani ajejwe kwivuna abansi Yasukazu Hamada avuga ko iyo misire yari ifise ubushobozi bwo gushika muri Amerika kandi ko yoguruka gushika ku birometero 15
000
 Kishida yabwiye abanyamakuru muri Thailand  ati: “Twabwiye (Pyongyang) ko tudashobora na gato kwihanganira ibintu nk’ibi”
 Ingendo ya Korea ya Ruguru mu mezi aheze ni iyo kurasa ibisasu vya misire mu kwihora ibikorwa vya gisirikare vya Amerika mu micungararo y’ikigwa ca Korea
 Iriko irahingura ubundi bwoko bwa misire iraswa kure, izwi nka Hwasong-17, ikaba ari ndende gusumba misire za ICBM imaze kugerageza muri kahise
 Abahinga bemeza ko imaze kugerageza kurasa Hwasong-17 incuro zitari nke ariko bikanka, kandi ko Pyongyang itarashobora kuyitunganya neza ku buryo yoguruka gushika aho yagenewe
 Mu ntango za kuno kwezi, igisasu ca ICBM carakwamiye mu nzira, nk’uko bivugwa n’igisirikare ca Korea y’Epfo
 Mu kw’icumi, Korea ya Ruguru yararekuye igisasu ca misire kiraswa kure hejuru y’Ubuyapani,  bwari bwo bwa mbere mu myaka itanu
 N’aho yafatiwe ibihano vyayimugaje, Pyongyang yaragerageje ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri incuro zitandatu hagari ya 2006 na 2017, ikaba izwi ko iriko irategura irigira indwi
 Ibandanya kandi yongereza ubushobozi bwayo bwa gisirikare

Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zashinze ko, uwo mu vy’ukuri ari we mutegetsi wa Arabia Saoudite-Umuganwa Samuragwa Mohammed bin Salman -afise ubudahangarwa ku rubanza yashingishirijwe n’umu- fiancée w’umunyamakuru yagandaguwe Jamal Khashoggi
 Khashoggi, yari azwi  cane nk’umuntu anegura ubutegetsi bwa Arabia Saoudite, yagandaguriwe mu biro vy’ubuserukizi bw’ico gihugu muri Istambul mu kwezi kw’icumi mu 2018
 Iperereza rya Amerika ryavuze ko ryibaza ko Umuganwa Mohammed ari  we yategetse ko uwo mumenyeshamakuru yicwa
 Ariko mu nyandiko bwarungitse muri sentare, ubushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire ya Amerika n’amakungu bwavuze ko afise ubudahangarwa bivanye n’amabanga mashasha afise y’umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Uwari umu- fiancée wa Khashoggi, Hatice Cengiz, yanditse kuri Twitter ko “Jamal yongeye gupfa uyu munsi” kubera iyo ngingo
 We- hamwe n’ishirahamwe riharanira uburenganzira bwa zina muntu Democracy for the Arab World Now (Dawn), ryashinzwe na Khashoggi – bariko bararondera indishi itamenyeshejwe uko ingana muri Amerika kuri uwo muganwa  samuragwa kubera urupfu rw’umu- fiancé wiwe
 Ico kirego cagiriza uwo mutegetsi n’abo bafashanya kuba "baranyuruje, baraboha, barakwega, barica urubozo, hanyuma baragandagura Jamal Khashoggi", yari umumenyeshamakuru n’uwurwanira demokrasi yaba muri Amerika
 Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Amnesty International , Agnes Callamard, yavuze ati: “Uyu munsi ni ubudahangarwa
 Vyose biganisha ku kudahana
” Umuganwa Mohammed yagenywe kuba umuganwa samuragwa na se, Umwami Salman bin Abdulaziz Al Saud, mu 2017
 Uwo mugabo w’imyaka 37 yaciye ahabwa amabanga y’umushikiranganji wa mbere mu kwezi kw’icenda uyu mwaka
 Arahakana uruhara urwari rwo rwose mw’iyicwa rya Khashoggi
 Abashingwamanza b’ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane bavuze ko “nk’umukuru wa reta y’ikindi gihugu ari mu mabanga ,”umuganwa samuragwa afise ubudahangarwa bw’umukuru w’igihugu hisunzwe amategeko ya sentare za Amerika nk’ingaruka z’ayo mabanga
” Ariko reta ya prezida Biden  yashatse gusigura ko iyo ngingo itavuze ko ari ukwemeza ko ata caha cakozwe
 Arabia Saoudite yavuze ko uwo yahoze ari umumenyeshamakuru wa Washington Post yari yishswe mu “gikorwa kitazwi n’abategetsi” n’umugwi w’abakozi bari barungitswe kumwumvisha ko yotaha mu gihugu
 Ariko, abategetsi ba Amerika bavuga ko iperereza rya CIA ryanzuye, “ku rugero ruri hagati no hejuru rw’uko ari vyo”, ko MBS – nk’uko uwo muganwa azwi – yari abifisemwo uruhara
 Iryo gandagurwa ryarababaje amakungu hanyuma ryonona rinacafuza ishusho ry’umuganwa Mohammed n’iy’igihugu ciwe
 Ryatumye kandi imigenderanire ya Amerika na Arabia Saoudite isubira hasi, aho prezida Biden yarahiye ko “azoharira ivomo” ico gihugu igihe yariko ariyamamariza ikibanza c’umukuru w’igihugu mu 2019
 Biden yaranse kuvugana na Mohammed bin Salman akiba umukuru w’igihugu
 Ariko muri iri ici, prezida Biden yavuze ko ashaka “gusubiramwo intumbero” y’imigenderanire, imbere y’urugendo yagize muri Arabia Saoudite mu kwezi kw’indwi
 Urwo rugendo, aho yafotowe ariko aramukanya n’uwo muganwa bakozanyako ibipfunsi – rwaraneguwe ko ari nk’urwo gushigikira reta ya Arabia Saoudite inyuma y’igandagurwa rya Khashoggi
 Sarah Leah Whitson, umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa wa Dawn, yanditse kuri Twitter ati “birenze agashinyaguro kuba prezida Biden we wenyene  yatumye MBS akwepa kubazwa ivyo yakoze mu gihe ari prezida Biden ubwiwe yari yemereye abanyamerika ko azokora ibishoboka vyose kugira yishure ivyo yakoze
 Ingingo yo ku wa kane yahaye uwo mutegetsi wo mu Arabia Saoudite “uruhusha rwo kwica”, ku bw’umuhungu w’umunya-Arabia Saoudite yahoze ari mu bajejwe umutekano ubu akaba ari mu buhungiro Saad al-Jabri, yagirije umushikiranganji wa mbere gutota umuryango wiwe no kurungika muri Canada abantu bo kuja kumwica
 Nihad Awad, umoyobozi ku rwego rw’igihugu muri  Council on American-Islamic Relations [Inama ku migenderanire ya Amerika na Islam], yavuze ati ubutegetsi bwa Biden bwagujije amaraso ya  Jamal Khashoggi n’ibitoro vya Arabia Saoudite”

