 Ariko aba-Democrats bazobandanya biganziye inama nkenguzamateka
 Haracasigaye intebe nkeya zo guhiganira
 Abarepubulika ntibavyifashemwo neza muri ano matora yabaye mu ndwi iheze, mu gihe bari bizeye ko bari gushobora kwiganzira inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka
 Ariko ejo ku wa gatatu baratsindiye intebe bari bakeneye kugira biganzire inama nshingamateka igihe Mike Garcia asubiriye gutsindira intebe y’akarere ka 27 k’intara ya California
 Ubu umugambwe w’Abarepubulika witeze gutsindira intebe hagati ya 218 na 223 muri ino nama nshingamateka igizwe n’abantu 435, nk’uko CBS ibitangaza
 Ariko, mu gihe ivyavuye mu matora bitaramenyekana mu turere tutari duke, ubwiganze bwabo bushobora kutaboneka neza mu kiringo c’imisi canke amayinga
 Kevin McCarthy yatowe ku wa kabiri n’abanywanyi basanzwe b’umugambwe w’Abarepubulika kugira ngo azosubirire umu-Democrat Nancy Pelosi nk’umukuru w’inama nshingamateka, yishimiye kubona inama nshingamateka ihindutse
 Ku wa gatatu mw’ijoro, uyu mushingamateka wo muri California yanditse kuri Twitter ati: "Abanyamerika bariteguriye inzira nshasha, kandi abashingamateka b’Abarepubulika bariteguye kubakorera”
 Kugira ngo ashobore gutorwa nk’umukuru w’inama nshingamateka, uyu mukuru w’inkehwa z’abarepubulika ategerezwa gushigikirwa na benshi muri ino nama nshingamateka yose igizwe n’abashingamateka 435
 Ariko umupfasoni Pelosi avuga ko adashobora kurekura uko nyene, aho mw’itangazo ry’ejo ku wa gatatu yavuze ko umugambwe wiwe uzotera “igitsure gikomeye bano ba Repubulika babasumba gato cane”
 Umupfasoni Pelosi, umugore wa mbere yagenywe muri iki kibanza, ntavuga muri iryo tangazo nimba ategura kubandanya nk’umukuru w’inkehwa, mu gihe i Washington havugwa vyinshi kuri kazoza kiwe
 Perezida Biden yakeje McCarthy amwemerera ko azokorana n’Abarepubulika ku nyungu z’Abanyamerika
 Ati: "Nk’uko nabivuze mu ndwi iheze, kazoza ni keza ku buryo kadashobora kugwa mu mutego w’intambara”
 "Abanyagihugu ba Amerika bakeneye ko tubakorera
 Bakeneye ko twitaho ibibazo vyabo ngirakamaro no kubaha ubuzima bwiza”
 Umugambwe wa McCarthy wari wizeye ko, kubona umukuru w’igihugu yari yataye icizere, ibiciro bibandanya biduga, vyari kubongerereza amajwi mu matora yo hagati muri manda
 Donald Trump  yahoze arongoye igihugu hamwe na Mitch McConnell  arongoye inkehwa z’Abarepubulika mu nama nkenguzamateka nibo bagirizwa ko batumye umugambwe wabo utavyifatamwo neza
 Ari iwe i Mar-a-Lago muri Florida, ku wa kabiri mw’ijoro, uyu yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu yaratangaje ku mugaragaro ko azosubira kwitoza mu kibanza c’umukuru w’igihugu mu 2024
 I Washington ejo ku wa gatatu, McConnell yasubiye kugenwa nk’umukuru w’inkehwa mu nama nkenguzamateka, maze abona kwikiza mugenziwe Rick Scott, umurepubulika wo muri Florida
 Amajwi atari ay’abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka arabandanya ashika buke buke inyuma y’indwi irenga habaye amatora
 Ejo ku wa gatatu, Karen Bass yaratsindiye ikibanza c’umukuru w’igisagara ca Los Angeles, igisagara kigira kabiri mu bunini muri Amerika, atsinze umutunzi ruhebwa Rick Caruso
 Uyu mu-Democrat agiye kuba umugore wa mbere atsindiye iki kibanza hamwe kandi n’umwirabure agize kabiri arongoye iki gisagara

Inyuma y’aho yagirijwe n’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya ko ari icanzo c’abimukira binjira muri uwo muryango, Serbia yafashe itegeko ryo gusaba visa abanyagihugu b’Abarundi n'abanya-Tunisia binjira muri ico gihugu
 Abanya-Turukia n’Abahindi nabo nyene biteze kubahamvya vuba
 Mu kw’icumi, Inama nkuru y’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya yavuze ko ishobora guhagarika uburenganzira bwa Serbia bwo kutariha visa mu kwinjira muri uwo muryango mu gihe yonanirwa no kuzibira abimukira bayikoresha nk’icanzo co kwinjira mu muryango w’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya
 Perezida Aleksandar Vucic yagiraniye ibiganiro n’abakuru b’ibihugu vya Autriche na Hongrie ejo ku wa gatatu, ari naho yemeye kurungika abandi bapolisi ku rubibe rw’ubumanuko, inzira nyamukuru y’abinjira mu gihugu badafise ivya ngombwa
 Mu misi iheze, hibonekeje Abarundi batari bake, cane cane urwaruka, baja muri Serbia, aho baca binjira mu bindi bihugu vya Buraya, aho benshi bavugwa ko bagana Ububirigi
 U﻿burundi na Serbia bifitaniye amasezerano y'uko abanyagihugu bavyo bashobora kuva muri kimwe baja mu kindi ata visa barinze gusaba
 Ariko ibintu vyahavuye biza guhinduka mu nyuma, aho hari abarundi bahuye n’ibibazo bashitse mu bihugu nka Turukiya na Qatar bagasabwa visa batari bafise bigatuma basabwa gusubira inyuma
 Mu kwezi guheze, L﻿eta y'Uburundi yaciye ifata ingingo yo kubuza Abarundi kuja muri Serbia no ku bafise impapuro z'inzira na visa
 Vyabaye inyuma y’aho ibihugu vya Buraya bitanguriye kwidoga kubera igitigiri c'abasaba ubuhungiro baciye muri Serbia cabandanya ciyongera
 Serbia ntiri mu muryango w’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya (EU/UE), ariko ibihugu bibanyi nayo nka Hongrie canke Roumanie biri muri uwo muryango bitanga amahirwe y’akazi, imibereho, n’uburenganzira ku mpunzi zibihungiyeho

Umunyarwandakazi Salima Mukansanga yizeye ko kuba yatowe ngo ahagarikire inkino z'igikombe c'isi 2022 bizofasha kwugurura imiryango ku bandi bagore bo muri Afrika bavyifuza
 Muri uyu mwaka, yabaye umugore wa mbere mu guhagarikira urukino rw'abagabo mu gikombe ca Afrika, mu gihe mu mwaka uheze yari yahagarikiye mu nkino za Olympic i Tokyo
 Uwo mugore w'imyaka 34 yizigiye ko kuba ari mu bagore batandatu ba mbere b'imboneza -hamwe na bagenziwe batatu b'abahagarikizi Stephanie Frappart na  Yoshimi Yamashita hamwe n'abunganizi b'abahagarikizi batatu nyene - mw'ihiganwa ry'abagabo bizotanga amahirwe ku bagore benshi
 Mukansanga yabwiye BBC Sport Afrika ati: "Ni iteka n'ibakwe kuko ntivyari bwigere biba"
 "Bivuze ko ugiye kuba uwa mbere kandi ugiye kwugurura umuryango ku bandi bagore, na cane cane abagore bo muri Afrika
" "Uba wiremetse  vyinshi ku bitugu vyawe, kandi  utegerezwa kuvyiremeka neza, kugira abandi babone ko umuryango wuguruye ubu bashobora kuwucamwo
 "Biraryoshe kandi ni amahirwe abagore baronse
 Bisigura ko amahiwe ahari - ni twebwe rero dutegerezwa kuyafata hanyuma  tukayakoresha mu gutera imbere
" Mukansanga asanzwe ari umumenyereza w'urwego rw'umupira w'amaguru kuva mu 2012, yavuye kure imbere yo gushika mu rwego rwa mbere rw'umupira w'amaguru  muri Afrika igihe yaja guhagarikira muri Cameroun
 Akiri umukobwa muto, yabwiwe ko atari bwakure bihagije kugira aje mu mugwi w'igihugu w'abatarakwiza imyaka 17 muri basketball gutyo aca ahitamwo gushimikira ku mupira w'amaguru
 Amaze akanya gato nk'umukinyi, yabonye itangazo ryo guhamagara abashaka kwiga ivyo guhagarikira - kandi nti bwari ubwa mbere -ati ivyo ntivyoncika
 Yaciye yegera urwego rw'Urwanda rw'umupira w'amaguru (Ferwafa) asaba kuja mu cigwa c'uguhagarikira buno nyene agiheza amashure yisumbuye ariko baramwankira, naho nyene bashingiye ku myaka yiwe
 Gutyo Mukansanga yacviye yiyigisha wenyene  ivyo guhagarikira, amategeko y'urukino, mu nyuma arahava arahabwa amahirwe na Ferwafa  yo kwigana n'abandi bashaka kuba abahagarikizi
 Iyo nzira itamworoheye ubu yamuvanye guhagarikira inkino z'abagabo mu gihugu ciwe c'Urwanda, ashika  mu gikombe ca Afrika c'abagore co mu 2016, mu gikombe c'isi c'abagore mu 2019 hanyuma no mu nkino za Olympic zabereye Tokyo
 Mu Buyapani yahagarikiye inkino z'abagore z'Ubwongereza na Chili  na Australia n'urwa Hollande n'Ubushinwa
 Itariku 18 ukwezi kwa mbere  yanditse amateka  ari mu yatumye ashika ku ntabwe agezeko ubu
 Niwe yari ahagarikiye mu kibuga hagati urukino rw'abagabo rwahuza Zimbabwe na Guinea mu gikombe c'isi ca Afrika  cabereye muri Cameroun
 Mu gihe yari yabanje kwankirwa akatari gake hanyuma akakirwa ata gishika cinshi mu gisata gisanzwe ciganziwe n'abagabo, uwo munyarwandakzi yarahanganye n'intambamyi zijane n'uwo mwuga
 Asigura ati: "Dutegerezwa gukora cane, cane cane mu gisata ciganziwe n'abagabo
 Utegerezwa gukora incuro zibiri gusumba
 "Hanyuma ukaba uvyiyumvamwo cane, kuko udafise kuvyiyumvamwo, uca uruha hanyuma ukabiheba
 Ariko ntidushaka guheba
 "Dutegerezwa kuba twateye intambwe imbere hanyuma tugakorera hamwe, tugakira ico dushitseko hanyuma uruganba tukarufatanya
" Umwigisha mu vyo guhagarikira wo mu rwego rw'umupira muri Afrika (Caf) Jerome Damon yemeza ko Mukansanga aho ageze ahakwiye vy'ukuri, kuba yahagarikiye inkino za mbere zikomeye ku rwego rw'umugabane wose  haba mu bagabo canke mu bagore
 Damon avuga ati: "Ni intambwe y'igitangaza- ari mu kibanza kimuha amahirwe ata wundi afise aho ari umwe muri bake bashobora kuja mu gikombe c'isi c'abakuze mu bagabo no mu bagore"
 "Ntivyari bwabe muri kahise, ivyo bivuga vyinshi kw'iterambere ry'uguhagarikira muri Afrika
" Damon, yahagarikiye  mu  mahiganwa y'ibikombe bine vya Afrika, avuga ko abo bagore batandatu batowe  ubwa mbere muri kahise k'igikombe c'isi bashitse muri ivyo bibanza babikwiye -kandi hazorabwa cane ivyo bazokora kurusha ko ari ab'igitsinagore
 Ashimika avuyga ati: "Dukeneye gutahura ko kuba abagore bashizwe mu mahiganwa bitabaye kubera ari abagore
 Ni ukubera babishoboye, kuko ari abahagarikizi ku rwego rwo hejuru"
 Mukansanga azoba ari kumwe muri Qatar na  Frappart wo mu Bufaransa na Yamashita wo mu Buyapani, hamwe n'abunganizi b'abahagarikizi Neuza Back wo muri Bresil, na  Karen Diaz Medina wo muri Mexique hamwe  na  Kathryn Nesbitt wo muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (US)
 Mukansanga ati: "Turashigikirana kuko tuva mu mihingo itandukanye ariko tugiye kuzokorera hamwe kugira abagore  bashobore "
 "Umugore ashigikiye uwundi mugore, nta keka muzobona umusaruro
 "Hari inzitizi, hari imitego hari ingorabahizi
 Tugiye guhangana n'ivyo
 Nta na kimwe dushobora kubikorako kiretse kuja kurugamba n'umutima uri hmwe, n'umwete hanwe no kwitanga - aho rero tuzoheza tubineshe
" Mukansanga yahagarikiye urukino rw'umupira w'amaguru ahantu hambere hakirurutse ku musozi wa Kilimanjaro muri Tanzania haraheze imyaka itatu, arazi ko i Qatar azoba ahanzwe n'amaso menshi kurusha uravye ingene igikombe c'isi ari ihiganwa rya mbere rikomeye muri uwo mukino
 "Abantu ntibashobora kwama bagushima, na cane cane uwutsinzwe
 Wewe ico ukora rero ni ugukora ico utegerezwa gukora - kuguma ku murongo, ntuje inyuma y'ingene amategeko y'umukino ategerezwa gutahurwa, uyakurikize hamwe n'ico urukino rusaba
 "Hanyuma , basubiye inyuma bakaraba, bazovuga bati, 'Ego, ivyo yakoze vyari vyo
"
