Uburusiya buriyamiriza burakaye cane akamo buterwa n’amakungu ko gutanga indishi y’akababaro ku vyo bwasambuye muri Ukraine
 Ibi bibaye inyuma y’aho Ikoraniro ry’ishirahamwe ONU ryemereje icemezo c’uko Uburusiya bukwiye kwemera inkurikizi z’ivyo buriko burakora, harimwo gutanga indishi y’akababaro
 Ivyemezo vy’ikoraniro rikuru bifise uburemere, ariko nta nguvu rifise zo kubishirisha mu ngiro
 Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya) ivuga ko izokora ibishoboka vyose kugira ibuze Uburengero kuyifatira amatungo ifise mu makungu kugira ntakoreshwe nk’indishi
 Umuvugizi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagiriza Uburengero ko buriko bugerageza “kwemeza ubusuma” no guhonyanga amabwirizwa agenga amatungo bwite n’amategeko mpuzamakungu
 Iki cemezo kivuga ko Uburusiya “butegerezwa kwemanga ingaruka ku bikorwa bibi vyose bukorera mu mahanga, harimwo gutanga indishi ku bubabare bwateje, harimwo ivyononekaye ivyo ari vyo vyose, kubera ibikorwa nk’ibi”
 Gisaba kandi ibihugu bihurukiye mw’ishirahamwe ONU gukorana na Ukraine bigashiraho igitabo mpuzamakungu co kwegeranirizamwo ivyemezo n’ibirego ku Burusiya
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine yakiranye yompi iki cemezo, akavuga ko indishi y’akababaro izorihwa n’Uburusiya ari “kimwe mu bigize ukuri gushingiye ku mategeko mpuzamakungu”
 Imbere y’uko iyi ngingo yemezwa, uwuserukira Kyiv muri ONU, Sergiy Kyslytsya, yabwiye abari muri iyo nama ko Uburusiya bwononye ibintu vyose muri ino ntambara, kuva ku mahinguriro gushika no ku mazu atuwemwo n’abantu n’inyubakwa z’ibitaro
 Hampande y’amafaranga akenewe yo gusanura ivyasambutse, avuga ko gukira ibikomere “bitazokwigera birangira hatabayeho ubutungane ku basinzikajwe n’intambara y’Uburusiya”, yongerako ati: “Harageze Uburusiya bwishura ivyo bwakoze”
 Uwuserukira Uburusiya muri ONU Vassily Nebenzia avuga ko iki cemezo “imbere y’amategeko ata na kimwe kivuze”, anagiriza Uburengero “kugerageza kudindiza no kwunyura intambara”
 Iki cemezo cashigikiwe n’ibihugu 94 kuri 193 bigize ishirahamwe ONU, mu gihe 14 – harimwo Uburusiya, Ubushinwa na Iran – vyatoye bigihakana
 Ibindi bihugu bisigaye vyose vyanse kwerekana aho bihagaze
 Tugereranije n’ubuheruka, ibihugu 143 vyaremeje icemezo mu kw’icumi co kwiyamiriza ingingo ya Moscou yo kwihagira uturere twa Ukraine mu buryo buteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Hariho uturorero tw’ibihugu vyategetswe kuriha indishi y’akababaro inyuma y’intambara
 Iyabaye rurangiranwa ni iy’imiriyaridi 269 y’amafaranga y’ama mark (yahoze ari amafaranga y’Ubudagi) ibihugu vyari vyishize hamwe vyategetse Ubudagi kuriha inyuma y’intambara ya mbere y’isi yose  - hafi imiriyaridi 300 y’amadorari y’abanyamerika muri kino gihe
 Ubudagi bwatangishijwe amafaranga menshi nk’aya mu ntumbero yo kuraba ko butohava busubira guteza iyindi ntambara vuba
 Ariko vyagiye kurangira bivuyemwo igihushane, kuko abahinga benshi mu vya kahise bavuga ko indishi zabumugaje n’ingingo yo “kwegeka icaha” ku Budagi, vyateje umujinya wagiye kwadukamwo intambara ya kabiri y’isi yose
 Ubudagi n’ibindi bihugu vyari bihurikiye hamwe kandi vyategetswe kuriha indishi inyuma y’iyo ntambara, ariko bashimikira cane ku gusanura ivyasambutse i Bulaya hakwibanda ku guhana Ubudagi ku bikorwa vyabwo

N﻿a Lindsay Brown Newsbeat Umugore wo muri Washington DC yashitse ku ndoto ziwe zo gutambana na Perezida  Barack Obama muri Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy'umukuru w'igihugu wa Amerika) yasandavye, afise imyaka 113
 Virginia McLaurin yari afise imyaka 106 igihe abonana n'umukuru w'igihugu wa mbere w'umwirabure ari kumwe n'umugore wiwe, hari mu 2016
 Ico gihe yabwiye Obama ati: "Ndakubwire, numva nezerewe cane
 Umukuru w'igihugu w'umwirabure, ego, n'umugore wiwe w'umwirabure"
 Mu 2014, uyu mutamakazi yasohoye urwandiko rwazungurutse cane asaba kubonana n'umukuru w'igihugu
 Yanditse ati: "Nitwa Virginia McLaurin
 Mba i Washington DC
 Navutse mu 1909
" "Si ndigera mpura n'umukuru w'igihugu
 Si nigeze nibaza ko nari kubaho gushika aho mbona umukuru w'igihugu atari umuzungu kubera navukiye mu bumanuko kandi ntashobora kwiyumvira ko bishobora gushika
 "Ndanezerewe kandi noryoherwa cane ari nka hamwe nobonana na wewe n'umuryango wawe nimba vyokunda"
 Uyu yahoze ari umushonyi yabandanije ati: "Ndibuka ibihe imbere ya Perezida [Herbert] Hoover
 "Ndibuka tudafise umuyagankuba
 Nari mfise itara ryakoresha igitoro
 Ndibuka imodoka ya mbere ya Ford
 "Umugabo wanje yari mu gisirikare
 Nabuze umugabo wanje mu 1941
 Kuva ico gihe mba i Washington DC
 Naba ngaha igihe Martin Luther King yicwa"
 Muri video Virginia yavuze ko yari acibuka igihe c'imbere y'uko atangura ishure
 "Nari akana gato
 Nta mazi meza twari dufise muhira
 Twategerezwa kuja kuvoma mu kinogo
 Virginia McLaurin yavutse mu 1909
 None ubuzima bwari bumeze gute ku banyamerika ico gihe? Ariko ubuzima ku banyamerika bari bafise amamuko muri Afrika nka Virginia McLaurin bwari bukiri inyuma
 Yavutse ata burenganzira na bumwe yari afise
 Nico gituma yari aryohewe cane kubona yarabayeho akibonera - akongera agatambana - n'umukuru w'igihugu wa mbere w'umwirabure
 Hanyuma umwaka wa 1909 ntiwari mubi cane ku banyamerika bamuka muri Afrika
 Muri uwo mwaka Virginia avuka, niho hashingwa ishirahamwe  National Association for the Advancement of Colored People (NAACP) ryaharanira uburenganzira bw'abanyagihugu atari abazungu
 Igikorwa caryo ni "Uguharanira uburenganzira bwa poritike, indero, imibereho myiza n'ukurwanya ubusumbane hagati y'abantu mu vyo ubutunzi, be no kurwanya urwanko n'ikumira bishngiye kw'ivanguraruhu"

Z﻿ambia irasaba insiguro ku rupfu rw'umunyeshure yahora arwanira Uburusiya muri Ukraine
 I﻿co gihugu gisaba Moscou "gutanga inkuru vyihuta"  zijanye n'urupfu rwa Lemekhani Nyirenda
 Uwo munyeshure w'imyaka 23 wo mw'ishure kaminuza rya Moscow Engineering Physics yari mu gihano c'igipfungo c'imyaka icenda azira gufatanwa ibiyayuramutwe
 U﻿muryango wiwe ufise ibibazo vyinshi kuri urwo rupfu kandi ukaba wipfuza kuraba ko ikiziga ari iciwe
 N﻿yirenda yapfuye mu kwezi kw'icenda ariko Uburusiya ni ho bukibimenyesha reta ya Zambia
 U﻿buserukizi bwa Zambia muri Ukraine bwasanze ikiziga ca Nyirenda cajanywe mu gisagara ca Rostov-on-Don kiri ku rubibe rwo mu bumanuko bw'Uburusiya, nk'uko vyamenyeshejwe n'umushikiranganji wa Zambia ajejwe imigenderanire Stanley Kakubo ku musi wa mbere
 U﻿mushikiranganji Kakubo yagize ati: "Nk'umushikiranganji, jewe ubwanje nagumye mvugana, kandi nzoguma mvugana n'umuryango wabuze kugira bamenye ukuri kw'ido n'ido y'ingene uwabo yapfuye
" Se wiwe Edwin Nyirenda yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru rya Reuters ko u﻿wo munyeshure yariko arakora akazi asanzwe akora igihe atariko ariga, ko gutanga amakete igihe haza umuntu atamenye amuha ipaki irimwo ibiyayuramutwe S﻿e na we yagize ati: "Ntituzi" uwakuye umuhungu wanje mw'ibohero, anongerako ko umuryango gusa "waronse ubutumwa buvuye ku mugabo tutazi wo mu Burusiya yatubwiye ko hari icipfuzo umuhungu wacu  yasize yanditse, kandi dutegerezwa kuja mu Burusiya"
 Z﻿ambia yahora irungika abanyeshure kwiga mu Burusiya ku mfashanyo y'ico gihugu, nk'uko vyari vyagenze kuri Nyirenda
 U﻿ko yarekuwe ava mw'ibohero ntibizwi, ariko Uburusiya bwaremereye umwidegemvyo bamwe mu banyororo mu gihe na bo bokwemera kugwana mu ntambara ibahuza na Ukraine
 M﻿u kwezi kw'icenda hari amasanamu y'ibanga yagiye ahabona yerekana abacangero b'umugwi Wagner bariko bararondera abanyororo baja kugwana muri Ukraine
 M﻿uri iyo video umukuru wa Wagner, Yevgeny Prigozhin yaragaragaye ariko aratanga amategeko y'intambara, nko kudahirahira ngo utoroke canke kudakora imibonano mpuzabitsina n'abagore bo muri Ukraine, hanyuma aca aha abo banyororo iminota itanu yo kwiyumvira nimba bashaka kuja kugwana
 M﻿u buryo buteye amakenga, yabwiye abanyororo ko ashobora kubakura mw'ibohero bakomeye ariko ko atokwemanga ko azobagarukana bakomeye
 I﻿gihugu ca Zambia nticagize aho cegamira mu ntambara iriko y'Uburusiya na Ukraine, co kimwe n'ibindi bihugu vyinshi vya Afrika, ariko kivuga ko ciyamiriza intambara iyo ari yo yose

