N﻿a Sam Cabral BBC News, Washington Amakuru y’uko aba-Democrats bagumanye inama nkenguzamateka ya Amerika inyuma y’amatora yo hagati muri manda yatumye haba ukwagirizanya mu mugambwe w’aba-Repubulika
 Abanegura uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu Donald Trump bamwagiriza ko ari we yatumye baronka amajwi make, mu gihe abandi ba-Repubulika babishira ku mukuru w’inkehwa mu nama nkenguzamateka, Mitch McConnell
 Hagati aho, Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu wa Amerika) yerekanye ikimenyetso gikomeye ko Perezida Joe Biden azokwitoreza ikindi kiringo
 Urugamba rwo kurwanira Inama nshingamateka rworwo gushika ubu ntirurarangira
 Aba-Repubulika baracafise amahirwe menshi yo gutsindira inama nshingamateka, ivyogira ingaruka zikomeye ku migambi ya Perezida Joe Biden
 Hagati aho, ubwiganze muri ino nama bugenda bugabanuka mu gihe amajwi akibandanya guharurwa
 Mu mpera z’indwi iheze, ibinyamakuru vya Amerika vyatangaje ko aba-Democrats batsindiye intebe zibiri z’Inama nkenguzamateka muri Arizona na Nevada, ivyabahaye akaryo ko kubandanya bayiganziye
 Ejo ku wa Mungu, buramatari w’intara ya Maryland, Larry Hogan asanzwe anegura uyo yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu, yabwiye imboneshakure CNN ati: "Aya ni amatora agize gatatu yikurikiranya Trump atwononeye
 "Yavuze ko tuzoruhishwa no kwama dutsinda
 Jewe rero ndambiwe no gutsindwa”
 Ariko, umunyamakuru wa BBC muri Amerika y’Uburaruko, Anthony Zurcher, avuga ko ikibazo nyaco ari ukumenya nimba abanywanyi ba Trump bazomuhinduka mu minsi n'amayinga biri imbere
 Kahise katwereka ko umugambwe uramutswa Maison Blanche mu bisanzwe utakaza intebe mu matora yo hagati muri manda
 Amajwi y’aba-Democrats muri uno mwaka afatwa ko ari yo ya mbere menshi ku mugambwe usanzwe uri ku butegetsi mu myaka n’imiburiburi 20
 Umukuru w’inama nshingamateka Nancy Pelosi  yabwiye ikiganiro This Week c’imboneshakure ABC News ati: “Abahinga i Washington baguma batubwira ko tutashobora gutsinda kubera kahise, kahise, kahise”
 Ariko aba-Democrats “ntitwigera twemera ibivugwa n’abahinga” hanyuma bibanda cane cane “ku budasa hagati yabo n’abakeba babo”, nk’uko uyu mutegetsi mukuru w’aba-Democrat akomoka muri California abivuga
 Umupfasoni Pelosi yari mu bategetsi bake cane ku wa Mungu bashigikiye ko Perezida Biden yitoreza ikindi kiringo mu 2024
 Umuhanuzi mukuru wo muri Maison Blanche Anita Dunn yabwiye CBS News ko umukuru w’igihugu atarazwa ishinga n’ivyo “urundi ruhande ruriko rurakora canke uwundi mukandida ashobora kuba ariko arakora”, kandi ko vuba azotangaza ingingo yiwe
 Avuga ko ivyavuye mu matora yo hagati muri manda aheruka "bikomeye cane” ku migambi y’umugambwe kandi Biden abona ko ari we “muntu nyawe wo kubandanya intambwe tugezeko”
 Mu gihe Biden yokwitoreza ikindi kiringo, ashobora kuba mu rugamba nk’urwa 2020 na Trump yitezwe n’abatari bake ko kuri uyu wa kabiri atangaza ku mugaragaro ko azokwitoza mu 2024
 Igikorwa co gutangaza ko azokwitoza giteje icuka n’umutima uhagaze incuti ziwe za kera mu mugambwe, aho bamwe mu banywanyi b’uyu yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu bifatira mu gahanga abamunegura, cane cane umukuru w’inkehwa mu nama nkenguzamateka, Mitch McConnell
 Ku wa Mungu, Stephen Miller yahoze ari umuhanuzi wa Trump muri Maison Blanche yabwiye imboneshakure Fox News ati: "Isura y’umugambwe w’Aba-Repubulika yubatswe na Mitch McConnell si nziza, ntiryoshe, ntibonwa neza kandi n’abatora ntibayiyumvamwo”

N﻿a Simon Stone BBC Sport Cristiano Ronaldo avuga ko yumva yahemukiwe na Manchester United (Man U) kandi ko ariko arirukanwa muri uyu murwi
 Muri Myandagaro (8), Ronaldo yari yemeye gusigura ubuzima bwiwe i Old Trafford (ikibuga ca Manchester United) inyuma y’aho vyankiye ko ava muri uno murwi akimukira mu murwi ukina mw’ihiganwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere iwabo (Champions League), nk’uko yari avyizeye
 Uyu mukinyi w’inararibonye wa Portugal  yavuye mu gacerere mu kiganiro kirekire n’umunyamakuru Piers Morgan w’imboneshakure TalkTV yo mu Bwongereza
 BBC yashatse kumenya aho umurwi Manchester United uhagaze kuri ibi bivugwa na Ronaldo ariko ntaco urashikiriza
 Inyuma yo gutsinda Fulham kuri 2-1 mu rukino rw’ejo ku wa Mungu, Man U iza mu kibanza ca gatanu mw’ihiganwa ry’Ubwongereza, Premier League, muri uno mwaka wa mbere w’umumenyereza Ten Hag
 Abajijwe nimba abarongoye Man U bariko bagerageza kumwirukana muri uno murwi, Ronaldo yavuze ati: “Ego, si umumenyereza gusa [Erik ten Hag], hari n’abandi babiri canke batatu mu murwi
 Numva ko nahemukiwe”
 Asubiye kandi kubazwa nimba abategetsi bakuru b’umurwi bariko bagerageza kumwirukana, uyu mukinyi w’imyaka 37 avuga ati: “Ntaco bimbwira
 Abantu bategerezwa kwumva ukuri
 "Ego, numva ko nahemukiwe, kandi numva umengo hari abantu batankeneye hano, si muri uno mwaka gusa, ariko kandi no mu mwaka uheze”
 Ronaldo ntarasubira gukina kubera ingwara itazwi kuva aho Man U itsindiwe na Aston Villa 3-1 ku wa 06 Munyonyo (11) akaba ari we yari kizigenza
 Mu kwezi guheze, Ten Hag yaranse kumukinisha muri Premier League igihe Man U ija gukina na Chelsea, hari haciye imisi itatu yanse kuja mu kibuga nk’umusubirizi
 Ronaldo yabwiye Morgan ati: "Sindamwubaha kuko ntanyubaha
 Mu gihe utanyubaha, sinzokwigera ndakwubaha”
 Muri iki kiganiro, Ronaldo arabwira kandi Morgan ivy’urupfu rw’umwana wiwe w’umuhungu mu kwa kane n’ingene yakozwe ku mutima n’icubahiro abafana ba Liverpool bamuhaye mu rukino rwayihuje na Man U  i Anfield (ikibuga ca Liverpool) mu misi yakurikiye
 Ikiganiro cose kimara iminota 90, ariko Morgan yakuyemwo inkuru ntoya yandikiye ikinyamakuru The Sun aho biboneka neza ko Ronaldo asuzugura ingene yasanze Man U imeze kuva agarutse mu murwi n’impundu nyinshi mu kwa munani 2021
 Ati: "Nibaza ko abafana bakwiye kumenya ukuri
 Nipfuriza ivyiza uyu murwi
 Nico gituma naje muri Manchester United
 "Kuva [uwahoze ari umumenyereza] Sir Alex [Ferguson] agiye, nta terambere nigeze mbona mu murwi
 Nta na kimwe cahindutse
 "Ndakunda Manchester United, ndakunda abafana, igihe cose bari ku ruhande rwanje
 Ariko nimba bashaka kuyihindura…bategerezwa guhindura ibintu vyinshi, vyinshi”
 Ronaldo avuga ko abona ibintu co kimwe na Ferguson, ari na we yagize uruhara rukomeye kugira ngo asubire i Old Trafford avuye muri Juventus igihe vyaboneka ko yashobora kwinjira muri Manchester City
 Ronaldo yongerako ati: "Arazi gusumba abandi bose ko umurwi utari aho wategerezwa kuba uri
