 Bose barabizi
 Abantu batabibona…ni uko badashaka kubibona; ni impumyi”
 Ole Gunnar Solskjaer yahoze akinana na Ronaldo ni we yari umumenyereza wa Man U igihe uyu munya-Portugal asubira mu murwi, imbere y’uko asubirirwa na Ralf Rangnick hanyuma hakaza uwuhari ubu, ari we Ten Hag
 Rangnick yaje kumenyereza Man U avuye muri Lokomotiv Moscow aho yari arongoye igisata kijejwe ukwinonora imitsi
