Igisirikare ca Ukraine kivuga ko cateye intambwe zikomeye ku musi w’ejo mu micungararo ya Kherson, inyuma y’aho Uburusiya butangarije ko buriko burakura ingabo muri ico gisagara co mu bumanuko
 Ingabo za Ukraine zivuga ko zabohoje igisagara gikomeye ca Snihurivka kiri ku birometero 50 mu buraruko bwa Kherson
 Kyiv (umugwa mukuru wa Ukraine) ivuga kandi ko iriko irasatira bikomeye ku mpande zibiri hafi ya Kherson, harimwo gutera intambwe y’ibirometero indwi mu turere tumwe tumwe
 Uburusiya buvuga ko bwatanguye kuva muri ico gisagara – igisagara gikomeye cane bwari bwigaruriye muri ino ntambara – ariko iki gikorwa gishobora gufata amayinga
 Itangazo ryo ku wa gatatu ryabonetse nk’inzitizi zikomeye ku ntambara ya Moscou muri Ukraine, n’aho abategetsi ba Ukraine bari bagifise impungenge – bagabisha ko ayo ashobora kuba ari amayeri yo kubatega umutego
 Nta cemezo cashotse kiboneka ko Uburusiya buriko burakura ingabo ku bwinshi muri Kherson
 Ejo ku wa kane, umukuru w’ingabo za Ukraine, Valeriy Zaluzhny, yavuze ko adashobora kwemeza canke guhakana ivyo kuva muri Kherson – ariko akavuga ko ingabo ziwe zateye intambwe
 Jenerari Zaluzhny avuga ko ingabo ziwe zateye intambwe zikomeye ku mpande zibiri ku ruhande rw’uburengero bw’uruzi Dnipro – akarere karimwo Kherson – mu kwigarurira ibibanza 12
 Ejo ku wa kane nyene, yavuze ko akarere k’ibirometero indwi kabohojwe “muri uno musi uheze”, mu gihe ingabo zariko zisatira amaja ku ruhande rwo mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko hamwe no ku ruhande rw’uburengero
 Amashusho ya videwo yerekana abanyagihugu bariko baramutsa abasirikare mu kibanza c’ihuriro, bigaragara ko bari bahejeje kwinjira mu gisagara ca Snihurivka
 Snihurivka iri ku masanganzira y’amabarabara akomeye kandi ni igituro ca gari ya moshi c’intara ya Mykolaiv, ihana urubibe na Kherson mu buraruko no mu burengero
 Ubutegetsi bw’intara ya Mykolaiv bwacishije ubutumwa ku rubuga hwaniro rwa Telegram buvuga buti “amakuru menshi meza uno musi”
 Bwaciye butuma haba ibihuha vyinshi mw’ijoro ry’ejo ku wa kane vyavuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zashitse mu nkengera za Kherson
 Iki cafashwe nk’ikimenyetso c’uko ingabo zishobora kuba zari zashitse mu kigwati ca Chornobayivka kiri mu micungararo ya Kherson
 BBC ntivyayishobokeye guhinyuza aya makuru y’uturere twabohojwe n’utwatakaye – ariko aya makuru aje inyuma y’amayinga ingabo za Ukraine zivuga ko zari zimaze zisatira
 Kherson ni wo mugwa mukuru wa mbere kandi wonyene w’intara waguye mu minwe y’Uburusiya kuva butanguye igitero kuri Ukraine ku wa 24 ruhuhuma (2)
 Kuva mu mpera z’ukw’icenda, yafatwa na Kremlin nk’Ubutaka bw’Uburusiya  - inyuma y’iciswe “amatora ya kamarampaka” mu turere twa Ukraine twigaruriwe n’Uburusiya, amatora yiyamirijwe cane n’amakungu
 Ku wa gatatu, Moscou yavuze ko bitari bigishoboka gukorera muri ico gisagara, ikavuga ko yategerezwa kwimuka ikava mu burengero bw’uruzi Dnipro - uruzi rucamwo kubiri Ukraine
 Jenerari Zaluzhny, umukuru w’igisirikare ca Ukraine, avuga ko ata kundi Uburusiya bwari kugira atari uguhunga, inyuma y’aho amayira yo gushikana uburyo asenyuriwe, uburyo bwo kurongora urugamba nabwo bukononekara
 Mu masaha yitereye y’ejo ku wa kane, umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi yavuze ko bizofata n’imiburiburi indwi yose kugira ngo Uburusiya bukure ingabo zabwo zose muri Kherson kandi ko bitoroshe kumenya ivyo umwansi ategekanya
 Jens Stoltenberg, umukuru w’urunani rwa gisirikare OTAN/NATO ruhurikiyemwo ibihugu vy’Uburengero, avuga ko biboneka ko Uburusiya “buri ku gitsure gikomeye” ariko ko bikenewe kuraba “ingene ibintu bigenda ku rubuga”
 Umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza wo kwivuna abansi, Ben Wallace, avuga ko Uburusiya buriko busa n’ubwubaka uruzitiro rwo kwivuna umwansi ku rundi ruhande rw’uruzi Dnipro bukoresheje ibikoresho bikomeye
 Avuga kuri iyi ngingo yo gusubira inyuma, Wallace avuga ko "amakungu adategerezwa gushimira Uburusiya ko buriko burasubiza amatungo bwanyaze”
 Umuhanuzi wo mu biro vya perezida wa Ukraine avuga ko hakiri kare kwigina  - akagiriza umwansi wiwe ko ariko ashaka guhindura Kherson akayigira “igisagara c’urupfu” mu gusiga ateragiye ama mine no mu gutegura kuyitera amabombe ari kure
 Ibi bishobora gutuma igitigiri c’abagwa muri ino ntambara ciyongera, mu gihe imaze guhitana canke gukomerekeramwo abasirikare 100
000 kuri buri ruhande n’abasivire 40
000, nk’uko biherutse gushikirizwa mu biharuro ngereranyo  bitangwa n’intwazangabo yo mu gisirikare ca Amerika
 Mu yandi makuru, Amerika yatangaje iyindi mfashanyo ya gisirikare igenewe Ukraine ifise agaciro k’imiriyoni 400 z’amadorari y’amanyamerika – harimwo ubuhinga bwa Avenger bwo gucungera ikirere hamwe n’ibisasu vya misire vyo mu bwoko bwa Hawk
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko yavuganye kandi n’umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubwongereza Rishi Sunak ku vyerekeye imfashanyo bwoha Ukraine mu rwego rwo kwivuna umwansi

Reta ya Ethiopia ivuga ko ingabo z’igihugu ubu zigenzura ahangana na 70 % h’intara ya Tigray iri mu buraruko bw’igihugu, ivyo umutegetsi wo muri iyo ntara igeramiwe n’ntambara yamirira kure
 Umuhanuzi w’umushikiranganji wa mbere mu vyo umutekano, Redwan Hussien, yanditse kuri Twitter ko “70% ya Tigray igenzurwa n’ingabo za Ethiopia”
 Avuga  kandi ko imfashanyo ziriko “zirinjira ku rugero rutari bwigere ruhaho”, harimwo no mu turere avuga ko tutagenzurwa n’ingabo za reta
 Umuvugizi w’umugambwe Tigray People's Liberation Front (TPLF), Getachew Reda, arahakana aya makuru nk’uko vyandikwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP
 Getachew asubirwamwo avuga ati: "Ivyo avuga abikura mu kirere”
 Abaserukira Tigray na reta ya Addis Abeba bari bagize imisi mu biganiro muri Kenya muri ino ndwi kugira bavugane ingene boshira mu ngiro amasezerano y’amahoro yateweko igikumu mu ndwi iheze muri Afrika y’Epfo
 Izi mpande zompi zarateye igikumu kuri ano masezerano ziyemeza kurangiza intambara zimaze imyaka ibiri muri Tigray
 Mu yandi makuru, ababibonye babwiye BBC ko abasivire batari bake bishwe mu gitero c’indege mu gisagara ca Mandi kiri mu burengero bwa Ethiopia
 Ababa muri ako karere bavuga ko ico gitero cabaye mu masaha yo gufungura ku wa gatatu muri ico gisagara kimaze imisi kigenzurwa n’abarwanyi b’umuhari w’inyeshamba za Oromo Liberation Army (OLA) inyuma yo gutana mu mitwe n’ingabo za reta
 Umunyagihugu atashatse ko izina ryiwe rimenyekana yabwiye BBC ko reta yashaka gutera inyeshamba ariko ko benshi mu bapfuye n’abakomeretse ari abasivire
 Umuvugizi wa OLA, Oda Tarbi, avuga ko abasivire 30 ari bo bapfuye, ariko ntavuga igitigiri c’abarwanyi bayo bishwe
 Abanyaporitike bariyamiriza iki gitero c’umuhari OLA bavuga ko ari ic’”ubugome”, bagasaba na reta kudakora ibitero ku basivire
 Reta ya Ethiopia ntaco iravuga kuri ibi
 BBC yagerageje kuvugana n’umukuru w’igisata kijejwe umutekano mu ntara ya Oromia, ariko yanse kugira ico ashikirije

Kimwe mu bigo vy’ubugenzuzi vya Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kivuga ko kiriko kirakurikiranira hagufi ingene ibintu biriko biragenda muri Twitter "n’impungenge nyinshi"
 Ni inyuma y’aho hari abakozi bo ku rwego rwo hejuru mu bajejwe amabanga hamwe no kwubahiriza amategeko bavugwa ko batanze imihoho
 Umurwi w’igihugu ujejwe ubucuruzi (Federal Trade Commission,FTC) uvuga ko umukuru w'urwo rubuga mushasha Elon Musk atari  "hejuru y’amategeko "
 Mu yandi makuru, Musk avugwa ko yoba yarabwiye abakozi ko n’ivyo kwugara bishoboka
 Iyi kompanyi iri mu mayira abiri kuva aho Musk atanguriye kwirukana ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’abakozi mu ndwi iheze
 Ubushobozi bwo kugura 'status' ku bakoresha uru rubuga mu gihe ari uwiyandikishije gushasha bwongereje impungenge ko Twitter ishobora kwuzura ama konte y’ibinyoma
 Ejo ku wa kane, Yoel Roth, yari arongoye igisata ca Twitter kijejwe umutekano yashize umwidondoro mushasha kuri runo rubuga hwaniro amenyesha ko atakiri muri ico kibanza
 Amakuru avuga ko umukuru w’igisata kijejwe amakuru y’ibanga Damien Kieran be n’umukuru w’igisata kijejwe ivyo kwubahiriza amategeko Marianne Fogarty batanze imihoho
 N’uwujejwe umutekano muri iyo kompanyi Lea Kissner na we nyene yaratanze imihoho
 Kubona aba bantu baragiye bishobora kwongereza ivyago vya Twitter vyo guhonyanga amabwirizwa y’ubugenzuzi
 Mu kwezi kwa gatanu, iyi kompanyi yaraciwe ihadabu ry’imiriyoni 150 kubera kugurisha amakuru y’abayikoresha, bikaba vyabaye ngombwa ko yemera ko hashingwa ayandi mabwirizwa mashasha ajanye no gucungera amakuru y’ibanga
 Douglas Farrar, umukuru w’igisata kijejwe imigenderanire muri FTC, avuga ati: "Turiko turakurikirana ibiherutse kuba kuri Twitter n’impungenge nyinshi”
 "Nta muyobozi canke ikompanyi iri hejuru y’amategeko, kandi amakompanyi ategerezwa gukurikiza ivyo twemeranije”
 Farrer avuga ko FTC ifise “ibikoresho bishasha biyiha ubushobozi bwo kugenzura ko kompanyi iriko ikurikiza ivyo yiyemeje kandi turiteguye kubikoresha”
 Twitter yarishe ihadabu mu kwezi kwa gatanu inyuma yo kwagirizwa ko yari yagurishije mu buryo buteye kubiri n’amategeko amakuru y’ibanga y’abayikoresha kugira biyifashe kugurisha amatanganzo yo kwamamaza
 Iruhande y’iri hadabu, yategerejwe kwemera amabwirizwa mashasha, kandi ikemera gushiraho umugambi  ukomeye wo gucungera amabanga n’umutekano vy’abayikoresha – bigenzurwa n’aba bategetsi bavugwa ko batanze imihoho
 Kuva afashe mu minwe Twitter, Musk yarirukanye uwahoze ari umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa Parag Agrawal hamwe n’abandi bategetsi bo hejuru, mbere n’abajejwe ibikorwa vyo kwamamaza n’amasoko na bo nyene baragiye
 Ibi vyose biza kwongereza amakenga kuba Twitter idafise abantu bakwiye bashobora gucungera nimba ibandanya igendera ku mategeko ngenderwako
 Vyongeye, amwe mu makompanyi makuru makuru yamamaza yaratewe ubwoba n'inzira Musk ariko atwaramwo iyi kompanyi y’urubuga hwaniro
 Twitter yinjiza amafaranga yayo hafi yose biciye mu kwamamaza, ariko amakompanyi amwe amwe yabaye arabangira kurekura amahera yayo, mu gihe acihweza impinduka Musk ariko arazana
 Amakompanyi amwe amwe avugwa ko afise amakenga ko Musk azodegura mu mategeko yo kugenzura ibica ku rubuga rwiwe mbere anahindure ingingo zo kwugara imbuga z’abantu bamwe bamwe bateje ibibazo, harimwo na Donald Trump yahoze arongoye Amerika
 Bivugwa ko Musk yoba yarabwiye abakozi bari mu nama ko atabona neza kazoza k’ingene ubutunzi bwiyongera muri iyo kompanyi, kandi ko atawoshira kure guhomba burundu
 Twitter yarasabwe kugira ico ishikirije
 Urubuga ngurukanabumenyi The Verge ari na rwo rwasohoye ijambo ryose Musk yashikirije abakozi, ruvuga ko Twitter itagifise igisata c’ukumenyesha amakuru

I﻿gitondo cose, ifoto zagaragaye ku mbuga hwaniro zerekana ibice vyinshi vyasambuwe ku kiraro kimwe rukumbi kiva mu gisagara ca Kherson
 I﻿vyo vyatumye abandika ku mbuga hwaniro bakurikiranira hagufi iyo ngwano bavuga ko ivanwa ry'abasirikare b'abarusiya mu burengero bw'uruzi Dnipro ryarangiye
 U﻿yu musi, umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi, asubiwemwo n'itororokanirizo ry'amakuru rya Tass, yemeje ko abasirikare bose b'abarusiya bari mu burengero bwa Dnipro bajabutse ku rundi ruhande
 H﻿ari ku musi wa gatatu aho abasirikare bo mu rwego rwo hejuru mu mapeta bamenyesha ko bariko barava ku ruhande rumwe rw'urwo ruzi
 Ingingo yo gusubira inyuma n'incamugongo ku gisirikare c'Uburusiya gihanganye n'ibitero vya Ukraine
 P﻿rezida Vladimir Putin ntiyari mu bamenyesheje iyo ngingo ku mboneshakure
 Ku musi wa gatanu, u﻿bwo bushikiranganji bwavuze ko ata bakozi, ibigwanisho canke ibikoresho vya gisirikare bwatakaje kandi ko ata bikoresho na bimwe bwasize inyuma
 M﻿w'itangazo rya buri musi, igisirikare cagize kiti:"Kw'isaha 05:00 ya Moscou uyu musi, ivanwa rya basirikare b'abarusiya mu buryo bwa Dnipro ryarangiye
 "Igihe bariko baravanwayo, nta gikoresho na kimwe ca gisirikare canke ikigwanisho casigaye inyuma
 "﻿Abakozi bose b'abarusiya bavanyweyo, ntitwatakaje umusirikare n'umwe canke ibikoresho vyabo
" Iryo tangazo ryabandanije ridondagura urutonde rw'ivyo igisirikare c'Uburusiya cashitseko muri Ukraine mu masaha 24 aheze
 Kuri uyu wa kane, igisirikare ca Ukraine cavuze ko cateye intambwe zikomeye hirya y'ejo mu micungararo ya Kherson, inyuma y’aho Uburusiya butangarije ko buriko burakura ingabo muri ico gisagara co mu bumanuko
 Ingabo za Ukraine zivuga ko zabohoje igisagara gikomeye ca Snihurivka kiri ku birometero 50 mu buraruko bwa Kherson
 Kyiv (umugwa mukuru wa Ukraine) yavuga kandi ko iriko irasatira bikomeye ku mpande zibiri hafi ya Kherson, harimwo gutera intambwe y’ibirometero indwi mu turere tumwe tumwe
 M﻿u bindi vyabaye muri iki gitondo, mu gisagara kibanyi ca Mykolayiv - ku birometero 95 mu buseruko bushira uburengero bwa bwa Kherson - n'imiburiburi abantu batandatu bishwe inyuma y'aho misile iterewe ku kw'inzu y'amagorofa

Perezida Joe Biden wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika avuga ko ingingo y’Uburusiya yo kuva mu gisagara ca Kherson muri Ukraine yerekana ko igisirikare cabwo gifise “ibibazo bimwe na bimwe”
 Perezida Biden avuga ko yari yiteze iyi ngingo “mu gihe kanaka” kandi ko ibi bizotuma impande zompi “zihindura intumbero zazo” mu gihe c’imbeho nyinshi
 Kherson ni wo mugwa mukuru umwe rudende w'akarere wo muri Ukraine wigaruriwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Ariko ejo ku wa gatatu, intwazangabo irongoye urugamba muri Ukraine yavuze ko bitari bigishobora kubandanya bakorera muri iki gisagara
 Jenerali Sergei Surovikin, amaze amayinga make ahawe kurongora uru rugamba, yatangaje iyi ngingo ari kumwe n’intwazangabo nkurunkuru za gisirikare ku mboneshakure y’Uburusiya
 Yemeje ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zigiye kuva mu karere kose k’uburengero bw’uruzi Dnipro
 Ni uruhombo runini ku migambi y’igisirikare c’Uburusiya mu gihe gihanganye n’igitero co kwivuna c’ingabo za Ukraine
 Biden yavuze ibi mw’ijambo yashikirije ari muri Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu vya Amerika), inyuma y’amatora yo hagati muri mandat, amatora umugambwe wiwe w’aba-Democrat uboneka ko ugiye gutakarizamwo uburongozi bw’inama nshingamateka bugafatwa n’umugambwe w’aba-Repubulika batavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi bwiwe
 Abakeba biwe muri poritike baherutse kwiyemeza ko bazokwihweza gushasha ibijanye n’imfashanyo ya gisirikare n’iy’ubutabazi Amerika isanzwe iha Ukraine
 Biden avuga ko “biryoshe” kubona Moscou (umugwa mukuru w’Uburusiya) “yararindiriye gushika inyuma y’amatora” kugira itangaze ko ivuye muri ico gisagara
 Ariko avuga ko yizeye ko “ingendo yo gukorana n’imigambwe yompi mu guhangana n’igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine” izobandanya
 Ukraine yakiranye amakenga ingingo yo gukura ingabo hakurya ya Dnipro
 Perezida Vladimir Putin ntiyitabiriye iki gikorwa co gutangaza ingingo yo kuvana ingabo mu gisagara ca Kherson
 Ariko babiri mu ncuti ziwe zikomeye - mbere bahoze banegura ingene Uburusiya buriko buvyifatamwo muri ino ntambara – barashima iyi ngingo
 Yevgeny Prigozhin yashinze umurwi w’abacangero, Wagner, akaba n’incuti ya Putin kuva kera, avuga ko n’aho iyi ngingo atari “intambwe yerekana intsinzi”, ni nkenerwa “kutibabaza, kutaguma mu bwoba, ahubwo gufata imyanzuro no kwihweza amakosa”
 Umukuru wa Tchétchénie/Chechnya, Chechen Ramzan Kadyrov, avuga ko Jenerali Surovikin yafashe ingingo "nk’umujenerali nyawe wa gisirikare, adatinya kunegurwa"

P﻿rezida wa Amerika yiruhukije inyuma y'aho aba demokrate baburije aba republika  kuronka amajwi menshi mu matora yo hagati muri manda
 A﻿ba republika babura gato ngo biganze mu nama nshingamateka ariko Biden avuga ko "bataronse intebe nyinshi cane" nk'uko vyari vyitezwe, ku musi wa kabiri ku mugoroba
 U﻿mwe muri iyo migambwe ushobora gutsindira kurongora inama nkenguzamateka, intsinzi ikaba ihagaze kubizova mu ntara zitatu aho amajwi gushika ubu yegeranye cane
 Mu bisanzwe umugambwe uri ku butegetsi, ubu ukaba ari uw'aba demokrate, ukunze gutsindwa mu matora yo hagati mu kiringo ca mbere ca prezida
 A﻿bajejwe imikenyuro mu mugambwe w'aba republika bari bizeye intsinzi itagabanije, bafatiye kw'iduga ry'ibiciro birengeje mu myaka 40 n'ingene abemera politike yiwe bari ku rugero rwo hasi
 A﻿riko ibiharuro ngereranywa bivuga ko abitavye amatora boba bahoye aba republika utwigoro twabo two kubuza abantu gukorora imbanyi
 A﻿vugira ku kirimba c'umukuru w'igihugu White House, ku musi wa gatatu ku mugoroba, Biden yavuze ko ivyavuye mu matora "vyatumye yiruhutsa"
 Y﻿avuze ati: "Nibaza ko wari umusi mwiza kuri demokrasi
" Y﻿avuze ko icizere ciwe  cagaragaye, aca anebagura abamenyeshamakuru bari bagabishije ko abademokrates bazotsindwa bikomeye
 K﻿ubera inguvu ahawe n'amajwi aronse muri iryo joro atari yiteze, Biden yavuze ko ategekanya gusubira kwitoza mu 2024
 Biden agiye gukwiza imyaka 80 muri uku kwezi yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ati: "Intumbero yacu n'ugusubira kwitoza, ni yo ntego yacu
" H﻿agati aho, aba republika bari begereje kuronka intebe 218 bari bakeneye kugira bakure mu minwe y'aba demokrate inama nshingamateka
 M﻿u gihe aba republika botsinda mu nama (shingamateka na nkenguzamateka) iyo ari yo yose muri izo, bazoshobora kuburizamwo imigambi ya prezida
 I﻿biro vy'umukuru w'igihugu kandi biriko biritegurira amatohoza y'inama nshingamateka ku butegetsi bwa Biden
 B﻿iden yavuze ko yiteguye gukorana n'aba republika kandi ko ashobora gutunganya ibiganiro vy'impande zibiri mu ndwi iza
 A﻿riko prezida kandi yavuze ko abanye Amerika bashobora gufata amatohoza yose yoba arongowe n'aba republika "nk'urukino rutwengeje"
 U﻿mugambwe wose uza gutahukana intsinzi mu ntara zibiri kuri zitatu zikomeye za Arizona, Georgie na Nevada, aca aramutswa inama nkenguzamateka

I﻿tangazo risaba abanyeshure b'abigeme biga kuri kaminuza mpuzamakungu ya Kampala kwipimisha imbanyi canke babuzwe gukora ibibazo ryateye impari ku mbuga hwaniro
 I﻿ryo tangazo ryahanahanywe cane, mu nyuma rikaza kufutwa, ryasaba abanyeshure b'abigeme biga mu gisata c'ubwakirizi (Kuvyaza) n'ubuforoma kwipimisha imbanyi, mu gihe batabikoze bakabuzwa gukora ibibazo
 Catherine Kyobutungi arongoye ishirahamwe rya African Population na Health Research Center, yasangije abandi iryo tangazo ku rubuga rwiwe rwa Twitter
 Y﻿abwiye BBC ko yabateye ubwoba ko agiye kwitwarira iyo kaminuza kubira iyo nyandiko
 Dr Kyobutungi yavuze ko iyo ngingo ari iyo ubukoloni, ata ho ishingiye mu mashure ya kaaminuza kandi ko ica intege abapfasoni
 U﻿mukuru w'ishirahamwe UNAids Winnie Byanyima yavuze ko "bidashobora kwihanganirwa kandi ko biteye isoni"
 U﻿wundi muntu yanditse kuri Twitter yavuze ko "vyari bibabaje kubona inzego zigihanganye na politike yo gucinyiza abantu nk'iyo
" Iyo kaminuza iza yamaze gusohora irindi tangazo  risaba abaanyeshure bose kudaha agaciro inyandiko yabasaba kwipimisha imbanyi, ribasaba ahubwo kwitegurira cane ibibazo

Reta ya Repubulika y’intwaro Rusangi ya Congo (DRC) yirukanye umunyamakuru Sonia Rolley akorera itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters, inyuma y’aho yimiwe uruhusha rwo gukorera muri ico gihugu
 Reuters imenyesha ko mu kw’icenda, Sonia Rolley ari ho yandika asaba ko yokwemererwa gukorera muri ico gihugu kugira ngo ahagararire ibikorwa vya Reuters vyo kwegeranya amakuru muri Congo
 Ivuga kandi ko yanahawe uruhusha rwo gukurikirana amakuru ku nama yerekeye ibidukikije i Kinshasa mu kw’icumi mu gihe yari akirindiriye inyishu
 Ku wa kabiri, niho yahabwa urwandiko rumurengutsa ku biro vy’igipolisi bijejwe uruja n’uruza ku mugwa mukuru Kinshasa, akavuga ko baciye bamwaka igitabo ciwe c’inzira, baca bamwuriza indege ija i Paris iciye Addis Abeba
 Ashimira abamurungikiye ubutumwa bwo kumuhoza, Sonia Rolley avuga ati: "Ni bwo bwa mbere nirukanywe [mu gihugu] mu myaka 20 maze muri uno mwuga
 Ndacatangajwe no kuba uno musi bimbayeko muri Congo inyuma y'iyi myaka yose maze nkora amakuru


"
 Rolley avuga ko ata mpamvu yabwiwe yatumye hafatwa iyi ngingo
 Hagati aho, reta yoyo ivuga ko "dosiye yiwe yamutumye yisanga ari kubiri n’amategeko agenga abanyamahanga, rero yari abaye muri Congo mu buryo buteye kubiri n’amategeko"
 Ishirahamwe rikingira abamenyeshamakuru, Comité pour la Protection des Journalistes (CPJ), rivuga ko “kwirukana Sonia Rolley ari ikindi kimenyetso c’uko uburenganzira bw’ukumenyesha amakuru muri DRC bubandanya bwononeraka”
 Angela Quintal, umugenzuzi wa CPJ muri Afrika, avuga ati: “Abategetsi ba Congo bakwiye guhindura ingingo yabo yo kwirukana Rolley kandi bagahagarika ibikorwa vyose vyo guturubika abanyamakuru”
 Mw’itangazo ryacishijwe ku rubuga rwa Twitter, ubushikiranganji bwo kumenyesha amakuru bwa Congo buvuga ko ingingo yo kwirukana uyu munyamakuru ataho ihuriye n’ibijanye n’ubwigenge bwo kumenyesha amakuru, ariko ko ari ingingo ijanye n’ubutegetsi
 Buvuga ko dosiye yiwe  yihwejwe n’inzego zibijejwe zigasanga ntiyujuje ibisabwa n’amategeko, kandi ko iyi ngingo yamenyeshejwe uwo iraba hamwe n’ikinyamakuru camusabiye uruhusha rwo gukorera mu gihugu
 Reuters asanzwe akorera ivuga ko iriko irafasha Sonia Rolley mu gihe ikibandanya irondera insiguro mu butegetsi bwa Congo
 Mw’itangazo yasohoye ivuga iti: “Reuters izobandanya itangaza amakuru muri Congo mu buryo bwigenga kandi ataho yegamiye, nk’uko dusanzwe tubikora ahandi hose kw’isi”
 Amakuru avuga ko yurijwe indege adatwaye utwiwe, mbere ko n’igitabo c’inzira yagiye kugisubizwa ashitse i Paris mu Bufaransa

Umu jenerari mukuru kurusha abandi bose muri Amerika agereranya ko abasirikare 100
000 ba Ukraine na 100
000 b’Uburusiya bamaze  gupfa canke gukomereka mu ntambara muri Ukraine
 Gen Mark Milley, umukuru w’ibiro bikuru vy’ingabo muri Amerika, yanavuze ko hafi abanyagihugu basanzwe 40
000 bamaze kwicwa bahitanywe n’iyo ntambara
 Ivyo bitigiri ngereranyo nivyo vya mbere biri hejuru bitanzwe n’umutegetsi wo mu bihugu vy’iburengarazuba
 Yavuze kandi  ko ibimenyetso ko Kyiv ifise ugushaka gusubira kuvugana na Moscou bitanga “akaberu” k’ibiganiro
 Muri iyi minsi ya vuba, Ukraine yarerekanye ibimenyetso vyo gushaka gusubira kuvugana na  Moscou, inyuma y’aho prezida Volodymir Zelensky ahebeye ivyo kuvuga ko uwo bahanganye , Vladimir Putin, ategerezwa kuvanwa ku butegetsi imbere y’uko ibiganiro vyongera kuba
 Yamara, Gen Milley, ari New York, yavuze ko kugira ibiganiro hagire ico bishikako, Ukraine n’Uburusiya vyompi bitegerezwa kwemera ko “intsinzi iciye mu ntambara  hari naho itoshoboka biciye mu buryo bwa gisirikare, ko rero mukeneye kuronderera mu bundi buryo
”  Uwo mujenerari mukuru -asanzwe ari we mujenama mukuru wa prezida Biden mu bibazo vya gisirikare – yavuze ko urugero rw’abo intambara ihitana rushobora kugondoza Kyiv na Moscou ko ari ngombwa  kuvugana muri aya mezi yimirije y’imbeho nyinshi, igihe kugwana bizogabanuka kubera ubukonje
 Ukraine n6’Uburusiya vyompi bibika kure ibitigiri vy’abapfa canke abakomerekera ku rugamba
 Ibitigiri vya nyuma vya Moscou vyo mu kwezi kw’icenda vyavuga ko abasirikare 5
937 bari bamaze kwicwa kuva  intambara itangura, umushikiranganji ajejwe kwivuna abansi Sergei Shoigu akaba yahakanye ivyavugwa ko igitigiri c’abapfuye kiruta aho
 Ibitigiri vya Gen Milley  biri hejuru  cane gusumba
