 Ariko mu kwezi kwa Myandagaro (8) umukuru w’ingabo, Valeriy Zaluzhniy, yasubiwemwo n’ibinyamakuru avuga ko abasirikare 9
000 bari bamaze kwicwa gushika ico gihe
