 ONU imaze guharura abantu miriyoni 7,8 bo muri Ukraine bahungiye i Buraya n’Uburusiya burimwo
 Ariko aho ntibarimwo abahunze ingo zabo yamra bakaguma imbere muri Ukraine
 Ku wa gatatu, Uburusiya bwamenyesheje ko ingabo zabwo zigiye gutangura kuva mu gisagara ca Kherson co mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko –igisagara gikomeye co nyene  caguye mu minwe y’ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Inkuru y’uko Uburusiya bugiye kuva muri Kherson ishitse mu gihe preziza Vladmir Putin muri Nyakanga (ukwezi kw’icenda) yahamagaje ingabo z’integabizoza  zishika 300
000 kugira zije kugwana muri Ukraine
