Imvune ya Sadio Mane yateje igipfungu intsinzi ikomeye ya Bayern Munich yaraye yirahiye Werder Bremen 6-1 mw’ihiganwa ry’Ubudagi, Bundesliga
 Vyabaye ngombwa ko Mane ava mu kibuga akaja kuvurwa inyuma y’iminota 20 kubera imvune yo mw’ivi, aca asubirirwa na Leroy Sane
 Ibi bibaye mu gihe hasigaye imisi 13 gusa imbere y’uko Senegal ya Mane ikina urukino rwayo rwa mbere mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi yose ca 2022 cimirije gutangura muri Qatar, ikazohura n’Ubuholande
 Hagati aho, Bayern yatahukanye intsinzi ikomeye cane, aho Serge Gnabry yateye bitatu wenyene
 Uyu musatirizi Mane yahoze akinira Liverpool yaciye agenda ubutarariye mu cumba c’ukwihinduriramwo amaze gusubirizwa kugira ngo abadanye avurwa
 Nk’umukinyi mwiza w’umwaka wa Afrika incuro zibiri, Mane ni kirumara mu murwi nserukira gihugu wa Senegal iherutse gutahukana igikombe ca Afrika mu mupira w’amaguru, aho uzohura n’Ubuholande mu rukino rwa mbere rw’itsinda A ku wa 21 Munyonyo (11), imbere y’uko uhura na Qatar yateguye iri higanwa, hanyuma na Equateur/ Ecuador
 Igitsindo ca nyuma ca Mane kuri penalty mu rukino rwa nyuma rwabahuje na Misiri catumye Senegal itsindira igikombe ca Afrika ku ncuro ya mbere, hari mu ntango z’uno mwaka
 Imvune ya Mane ntiyabujije Bayern gusayangana maze ishobora kurangiza inkino zo hagati muri ino ndwi ari iya mbere muri Bundesliga
 Jamal Musial ni we yinjije ica mbere ku munota wa gatanu w’urukino, ariko rero haciye akanya gato Bremen iragikurayo ku mupira mwiza bagiye bahanahana imbere y’uko Anthony Jung atsinda umunyegori Manuel Neuer
 Bayern yaciye ihindura umukino maze yinjiza ibitsindo bitatu mu minota umunani, aho Leon Goretzka  yijije kimwe, Gnabry nawe atera bibiri, maze mu minota 30 Bayern imaze kunyagira Bremen 4-1
 Ibintu vyari kuba vyamaze kuba nabi gusumba muri uwo mwanya iyo umunyegori Jiri Pavlenka adakurayo penalty y’umunya-Cameroun Eric-Maxim Choupo-Moting ku munota wa 17
 Bayern yabandanije yiyoroheje gushika mu mpera z’urukino, aho ku munota wa 82 Gnabry yinjije igitsindo ciwe kigira gatatu, ata n’akanya gaheze umusore w’umufaransa  Mathys Tel aca asongera isibe

Umu cardinali w’Umufaransa Jean Pierre Ricard yavuzwe izina na Ekleziya Katolika nk’umwe mu basenyeri 11 bagikorera canke bigeze gukorera iryo shengero bagirizwa guhohotera abana Mw'itangazo, uyo mu cardinali yanditse ko yahohoteye  umwana w'umukobwa w’imyaka 14 igihe yari akiri padiri kw'iparuwase haraheze  imyaka mirongo 35,  kandi ko ubu ashobora gukura meza mu mabanga yiwe
 H﻿araciye umwaka, umugwi washinzwe utoye ivyemeza ko hari ibihumbi n'ibihumbi vy'abantu bashurashuza abana, bakorera mw'ishengero Katolika ry'Ubufaransa mu myaka irenga mirongo ibiri
 Uko   bagirizwa ari 11 bose barashengejwe mu butungane canke bahabwa ibihano na Ekleziya Katolika
 I﻿bi vyagiye ahabona mu gihe mu gihe hariko haraba inama y'abepisikopi b'Ubufaransa i Lourdes, mu bumanuko bushira uburengero bw'Ubufaransa
 Musenyeri mukuru Eric de Moulins-Beaufort yabariye abamenyeshamakuru ko muri abo 11 harimwo Musenyeri wa Creteil Michel Santier yagiye mu karuhuko ko muzabukuru mu mwaka uheze inyuma yo kwagirizwa ihohotera rifatiye ku gitsina mu myaka  mirongo ibiri iheze
 Bamwe bariko bakorwako amatohoza ajanye n'ihohotera rifatiye ku gitsina  mu gihe abandi bagirizwa kubinuma
 Musenyeri mukuru yasomeye ku mugaragaro ikete rya Cardinali Ricard, aho yavuze ko yitwaye nabi "mu buryo bukwiye guhanwa" ku mwana w'umukobwa w’imyaka 14 kandi ko  mu vy’ukuri imyitwarire yiwe yagize ingaruka mbi kandi  zitazopfa zibagiwe kuri uwo mwana w'umukobwa
 Mu gihe ubu ari mu karuhuko k'iza bukuru inyuma y'imyaka 18 ari musenyeri wa Bordeaux, uwo mu cardinali w'imyaka 78 yavuze ko yamusavye ikigongwe kandi asaba n'imbabazi ku bantu bose yababaje
 M﻿usenyeri ahari ubu, Jean Paul James, yavuze ko yifatanije umubabaro n'abakorewe icaha, aca asubira gutera akamo uwo ari we wese yoba yarahohotewe muri iyo diyoseze kubivuga
 Umukuru w'imana y'abepisikopi yavuze ko kiretse uwo mu Cardinali na Michel Santier, abasenyeri batandatu bagirijwe n'ubutungane canke ishengero kandi ko  umwe aza yaramaze gupfa
 Yongeyeko ati:"A﻿bandi bahoze ari abasenyeri bariko baragirwako amatohoza n'ubutungane mu gihe uwundi wa gatatu amaze kwitaba abashikirizamanza
" Mu cegeranyo cayo co mu kwezi kwa 10 mu 2021 , akanama kigenga kashizweho na Ekleziya Katolika yo mu Bufaransa kasanze abana ibihumbi 216 barahohotewe kuva mu myaka ya 1950, benshi muri bo bakaba bari abana b’ababahungu bari gahati y’imyaka 10 na 13
 Umukuru w'ako kanama yavuze ko hari ivyemezo ko hari abakoze ihoterwa bashika 3
200 kandi ko ivyo vyemezo vyarahawe  abashikirizamanza mu mice 22 aho ingingo zo gukurikiranwa kuri ivyo vyaha zishobora gufatwa
 U﻿bufaransa ni kimwe mu bihugu aho ibivugwa ko habaye ihohoterwa rifatiye ku gitsina vyateye vyanyiganyije ishengero ya Ekleziya Katolika
 Mu mwaka uheze, Papa Francis yarahinduye amategeko agenga ishengero Katolika kugira ihohoterwa rifatiye ku gitsina, kwiyegereza abana ugamije kubashurashuza, gutunga ama film y’abana bariko barahuza ibitsina hamwe no gukingiranira ikibaba ku caha c'ihohoterwa, ko ari icaha gihanwa n'amategeko ya Vatikano
 Mu butumwa yatanze imbere y'uko hatangura iyo nama y'abepisikopi i Lourde, Papa yavuze ko ishengero ryo mu Bufaransa ryaguye mu gahundwe kubera ihohoterwa ryakozwe na bamwe mu bungere baryo
 I﻿yo nama yari ifise intumbero yo guteza imbere uburyo bwo guhanahana amakuru no gukorera mu muco ku mabi y'ihohoterwa ishengero rifisemwo uruhara

Umuhanuzi wa Reta zunze Ubumwe za Amerika mu vyo umutekano Jake Sullivan aremeza ko imihora yo kuyaga hagati ya Washington na Moscou icuguruye, n’aho intambara ya Ukraine ibandanya
 Mw’ijambo yavugiye i New York, Sullivan avuga ko ari “ku nyungu” za Amerika kubandanya ivugana na Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu w’Uburusiya)
 Ariko ashimangira ko abategetsi “bama barikanuye kubera uwo bariko baravugana”
 Ibi bibaye mu gihe Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu wa Amerika) idashaka guhakana amakuru avuga ko Sullivan arongoye ibiganiro n’Uburusiya mu ntumbero yo kubuza igitero ca nikleyei muri Ukraine
 Ikinyamakuru Wall Street Journal co muri Amerika kivuga ko Sullivan ibiganiro na mugenziwe w’Uburusiya, Nikolai Patrushev, umunyamabanga w’inama yigihugu ijejwe umutekano, hamwe na Yuri Ushakov, umuhanuzi mukuru wa Kremlin mu vyo imigenderanire, kuva mu mezi atari make aheze, yabigize ibanga
 Abategetsi bakuru babwiye iki kinyamakuru ko aba bagabo bavuganye ingene bokwirinda ikoreshwa ry’ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri mu ntambara yo muri Ukraine, ariko ko batigeze baja mu biganiro vy’ingene intambara yohagarara
 Mu kwezi guheze, Sullivan yavuze ikoreshwa iryo ari ryo ryose ry’ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri ryogira “ingaruka mbi cane ku Burusiya”
 Yabwiye ikinyamakuru co muri Amerika NBC ko, mu biganiro vy’ibanga bagiriraniye n’abategetsi b’Uburusiya, abategetsi bakuru “bashikirije” urugero Amerika yoshikako mu kwihora
 Umuvugizi w’inama nkuru y’igihugu ya Amerika, Adrienne Watson, yaranse kwemeza iyi nkuru, abwira iki kinyamakuru ko “abantu bivugira vyinshi”, mu gihe umuvugizi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagiriza ibinyamakuru vy’Uburengero "gutangaza ibinyoma vyinshi"
 Ariko umunyamabanga wa Maison Blanche ajejwe kumenyesha amakuru Karin Jean-Pierre yavuze ejo ku wa mbere ko Amerika ifise uburenganzira bwo kugiriranira ibiganiro n’Uburusiya
 Sullivan – uyu akaba azwi ko ari umwe mu bahanuzi bakuru ba Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika babandanya bahimiriza ibiganiro n’Uburusiya – avuga ko kubandanya bavugana na Moscou ari “ku nyungu z’igihugu ico ari co cose gikorwako n’iyi ntambra”
 Mu ndwi iheze, ikinyamakuru Washington Post catangaje ko abategetsi bakuru ba Amerika bariko basaba Kyiv kwerekana ko ifise ishaka ryo kugiriranira ibiganiro n’Uburusiya
 Basaba kandi Ukraine kutanka kuganira ivyo guhagarika iyi ntambara mu gihe Perezida Vladimir Putin azoba akiri ku butegetsi
 Ariko Sullivan yabwiye ikoraniro ryabereye i New York ko ubutegetsi bwa Biden “butegerezwa kubandanya ico bwiyemeje” kandi ko bwiyemeje gukorana n’incuti mpuzamakungu “kugira ngo abakoze ivyaha vyo mu ntambara bikomeye muri Ukraine barengutswe kugira ngo bishure ivyo bakoze”
 Sullivan  ati: "Nari i Kyiv ku wa gatanu kandi nararonse akaryo ko kuvugana na Perezida  [Volodymyr] Zelensky na mugenzanje Andriy Yermak, hamwe kandi n’abarongoye igisirikare, ndaronka kandi n’insiguro ku rugero rw’ubwicanyi n’ubwononyi vyatewe n’intambara ya Putin kuri ico gihugu”
 Kuva mu mezi aheze, amakenga yariyongereye ko Uburusiya bushobora kwikora ku birwanisho vya nikleyeri mu kugerageza gukingira intara zine zo mu buseruko n’ubumanuko bwa Ukraine bwihagiye mu buryo buteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Hagati aho, Ukraine yifashishije amategeko yo mu ntambra kugira ngo ifate mu minwe amatungo y’amakompanyi atanu makuru makuru
 Amwe muri ayo makompanyi – harimwo abiri y’amasoko ntanganguvu n’ayandi ahingura amamoteri, amamodoka n’ama transformateurs/transformers – afitaniye ubucuti n’umutunzi ruhebwa Vyacheslav Bohuslayev yahagaritswe yiketswe ko akorana n’Uburusiya
 Perezida Zelensky avuga ko iyi ngingo izofasha igisata ca Ukraine kijejwe kwivuna abansi kuronka vya nkenerwa mu gisirikare ubu kiri mu bikorwa vyo gutuza umwansi mu bumanuko n’ubuseruko bwa Ukraine

Na  Rob Haywood U﻿munyamakuru w'inkino wa BBC Ni iki ibikombe vy'isi vy'imbere y'aha bishobora kutwigisha ku vyo twokwitega muri  Qatar? Igikombe c'uno mwaka coba kigoye? Ibihugu vyaronse itike yo kuja muri iri higanwa bibanje gukina urukino rwa play-off vyohebuzwa ubu nyene? Ubwo gukinira muri Asia vyoba bizokworohera ibihugu bimwe bimwe? Turaraba ibi vyose - hamwe n'ibindi vyinshi - kugira turabe ibihugu bishobora guhabwa amahirwe muri kino gikombe c'isi yose c'uno mwaka
 Hamaze kuba amahiganwa atandatu ahuriyemwo igitigiri nk'iki c'ibihugu 32 bigabuwe mu mirwi umunani umwe umwe ufise ibihugu bine bine , akaba ari ayo mahiganwa atandatu aduha inkino 384 tugiye kwihweza kugira turabe niba hari ibija biragaruka
 Mu mwihwezo ukurikira, tugiye kurabiha hamwe aya mahiganwa atandatu - kuva mu 1998 gushika 2018 - - kiretse bibaye ngombwa ko tuja hanze y’aho
 Mu mahiganwa atatu aheruka kubera i Bulaya, mu bibanza 16 vyo muri ca gice co gukuranamwo (canke igice c’umunani gishira ica nyuma), imigwi y'i Buraya yafashemwo 10
 Iyo ihiganwa ribereye hanze y'Ubulaya, iki gitigiri caramanuka nko gushika ku ndwi
 Imirwi yo muri Amerika y'Ubumanuko niyo ica ihatomborera, mu gihe igitigiri c'imigwi ya Asia ishike muri ico gice yigwiza na kabiri  iyo ihiganwa ribereye hanze y'Ubulaya
 Ibikombe bitanu  ku mahiganwa atandaatu aheruka vyatwahanywe n'ibihugu vy'i Buraya -  kandi uretse Ubufaransa bwatsinze iri higanwa mu 1998 buronse itike kubera ari bwo bwari bwaryakiriye, ibindi vyose vyari vyitwaye neza mu mahiganwa yo kurondera itike
 Ibindi bihugu bine vyatahukanye iki gikombe - Ubutaliyano mu 2006, Espagne mu 2010, Ubudagi mu 2014 be n'Ubufaransa mu 2018 - wasanga birangije bidatsinzwe na rimwe canke ugasanga bitsinzwe nka rimwe gusa mu nkino cumi zo kurondera itike
 Urugero rw'izi nstinzi (mu gihe iyo banganije biharurwa nk'inusu y'intsinzi) rwari ku 80% no kurenga
 Mu nkino zo kurondera itike mw'ihiganwa ry'uno mwaka, ibihugu vyinshi vya Bulaya vyarashitse kuri uru rugero: Danemark (95%), Ubwongereza n'Ubudagi (90%), Serbia n'Ububirigi (87
5%), Espagne, Ubuswisi n'Ubufaransa ( 81
3%) hanyuma Croatia n'Ubuholande ( 80%)
 Twisunze urutonde rwa FIFA rw'ingene ibihugu bikurikirana kw'isi, turashobora kubona ingene iri higanwa rishobora kuzoba rikomeye
  Raba ubutandukane bw'ingene ibi bihugu 32 bihagaze kuri buri higanwa: Kubera amategeko ya FIFA agena igitigiri c'imirwi iva kuri buri mugabane, hari ibihugu bitari muri iri higanwa kandi ku rutonde rwa FIFA biri imbere ya bimwe mu vyaronse itike
 Ibihugu bikomeye bitazokwitabira iri higanwa ry'uno mwaka ni Ubutaliyano - buza mu kibanza ca gatandatu - ariko  Colombia (17), Peru (23), Suède (25), Ukraine (27), Chili (29) na Nigeria (32) vyari kuba vyararonse itike iyaba urutonde rw'isi ari rwo rwakurikizwa mu kugena abaryitabira hatarabwe aho igihugu giherereye
 Mu gihe ibihugu indwi vyo ku rugero rwo hasi biri muri rino higanwa bishobora kuboneka ko ari vyinshi, uravye ahubwo ni igitigiri gito kuva iri higanwa ritanguye guhuriramwo ibihugu 32
 Hari amahiganwa yagiye yitabirwa n'ibihugu bishika 11 biri inyuma ya 32 vya mbere
 Rero iki gihe ni ihiganwa rizoba rikomeye cane
 Hanyuma turavye ingene ibihugu bihagaze, biboneka ko Ubwongereza na Pays de Galles (Wales) biri mu murwi utoroshe na gato muri  Qatar - ni wo murwi wonyene uhuriyemwo imirwi iri muri 20 ya mbere dufatiye kuri uru rutonde rwo ku wa 30 z'ukwa cumi
 Imirwi yo mu gikombe c'isi yose ca 2022  n'ingene ibihugu bihagaze kw'isi (Gushika   ku wa 30 z'ukwa cumi
 ) Pays de Galles mu mahiganwa ya mbere yitabiriye mu myaka 64, yamye ironka itike ibanje gukina play-offs  kumwe na Pologne hamwe na Portugal
 Ukibibona ubwa mbere, womenga vyaciye mu canzo - ariko akahise ka vuba kerekana ko ibihugu bironka itike muri iyo nzira bikora ibintu bikomeye
 Tugereranije imirwi ya Bulaya, 67% y'ibihugu bironka itike biciye muri play-offs  birashika mu gice co gukuranamwo, ugereranije na 57% gusa biba vyaronse itike mu buryo bworoshe
 Inkino zibiri za nyuma (finales)  z'amahiganwa atandatu aheruka zahuje ibihugu vya Bulaya vyaronse itike mu ma play-offs - ibi bikaba ari Ubudagi mu 2002 hamwe na Croatia mu 2018
 Vyongeye, Croatia (1998) na Turukiya (2002) vyashitse mu  gice ca kabiri gishira ica nyuma (demi-finales) , mu gihe ibindi bihugu bitatu navyo vyashitse mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma (quart de finales)
 Kuva mu myaka ya 1990, mu bihugu biba bifise igikombe, ikimaze gutsinda muri  gice c'inkino zo gukuranamwo (knockout) ni kimwe gusa, iki naco ni Ubudagi igihe butsinda Ghana mu 2006
 Mu vy'ukuri, kuva mu 1962, nta gihugu kirashobora kugumana igikombe, mu gihe mu mahiganwa 14  kuva ico gihe, ibihugu bibiri ari vyo  vyonyene bimaze kugera mu gice ca kane gishira ica nyuma
 Ibihugu biba bifise igikombe kenshi bitangura kugira ingorane ku rukino rwa mbere
 Mu mahiganwa 12 kuva Ubwongereza butsinze urukino rwa mbere aho bwahura na Roumanie mu 1970, ibihugu bitatu vyonyene biba bifise igikombe ni vyo bimaze gutsinda urukino rwa mbere
 Mbere bine muri bitanu biba bifise igikombe nta n'uko vyavuye mu nkino zo mu mirwi (phase des groupes)
 Kubera iki? Imyaka ine ni igihe kirekire mu mupira w'amaguru
 Uravye, usanga 50% vy'abakinyi batsindiye ico gikombe ari bo batangura urukino rwa mbere rwo mu mirwi mw'ihiganrwa rikurikira
 Igihe Ubutaliyano bukina urukino rwa mbere bukanganya na Paraguay mu 2010, bwakinishije batatu gusa mu bari batsindiye igikombe ca 2006
 Nimba witeze ko imirwi ibiri ya mbere ari iyizoba ihagaze neza ku rutonde mpuzamakungu muri buri murwi, uzotangara
 Ni ibisanzwe ko bitandatu muri 16 bikina inkino zo gukuranamwo usanga bigira gatatu na kane mu mirwi yavyo
 Ni urugero rutangaje rwa 32%
 Muri ano mahiganwa atandatu nyene, imirwi yo hasi yatsinze inkino zo gukuranamwo ku rugero rwa 34%
 Inkino zitatu muri zine zababaje ni izatsinzwe n’ibihugu vyakiriye amahiganwa - ku ncuro zibiri biciye ku ma penalties, incuro imwe nayo biciye ku gitsindo c'inzahabu
 Uko bizogenda kwose mu ndwi zitanu ziri imbere, hashobora kuba ibintu bizobabaza abantu, bitangaza, eka ibintu bizoteza impari

Na Max Matza BBC News, Washington Perezida Joe Biden n’uwo yasubiriye Donald Trump bateguye amakoraniro akomeye yo kurwanira amajwi mu gihe imyiyamamazo mu matora agiye guha isura nshasha inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka yinjiye ku musi wa nyuma
 Ejo ku wa Mungu, Biden na Trump bakoreye imyiyamamazo yabo i New York na Florida umwe umwe
 Amahirwe menshi yimukiye ku ruhande rw’Abarepubulika bariko baragerageza kurondera kwigarurira impande zompi za Congres, ni ukuvuga inama nshintamateka n’inama nkenguzamateka, zompi zigenzurwa n’abo mu mugambwe w’aba-Democrats
 Bahabwa amahirwe menshi yo gutsindira Inama nshingamateka, ariko Inama nkenguzamateka ni itombora, nk’uko ibiharuro ngereranyo bivyerekana
 Mu gihe boramuka batsindiye uruhande rumwe, vyogira ingaruka zikomeye cane nteguro za Perezida Biden
 Mu gihe umusi wa nyuma w’imyiyamamazo ari uno wa mbere, umugambwe wiwe witeguye gutakaza mbere no mu turere mu bisanzwe twari utw’aba-Democrats
 Yashikirije ijambo mu myiyamamazo i New York ejo ku wa Mungu ashigikira buramatari Kathy Hochul ahanganye bikomeye, mu buryo atari yiteze, n’umu-Repubulika Lee Zeldin ashigikiwe na Trump
 Ku munota wa nyuma, uyu mupfasoni yagiye gushigikirwa n’amazina ya bamwe mu ba Democrats bakomeye cane - uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu Bill Clinton, icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu Kamala Harris n’uwahoze ari umunyamabanga wa reta ajejwe imigenderanire Hillary Clinton
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe, Biden yavuze ko aya matora ari "igihe co gufata umurongo" uzogena imyaka 20 iri imbere
 Yabwiye abatora kw’ishure kaminuza Sarah Lawrence College ko bariko baratora hagati “y’imbono zikomeye zibiri zitandukanye za Amerika”
 Ni mu gihe uwo yasubiriye muri Maison Blanche/White House, Donald Trump, yari i Miami aho yavugiye ijambo mu kiringo kirenga isaha, ahondahonda aba-Democrats, abagiriza ko bariko batwara igihugu mu ntwaro ya “gikomunista”
 Trump yabwiye abari aho ati: "Aba-Democrats bashaka guhindura Amerika bayigire Cuba y’abakomunista canke Venezuela y’abasosiyalisti”
 Abandanya ati: "Ku munyamerika w’umuhispaniya wese muri Florida no mu gihugu cose, turakwakirije yompi yompi yompi mu mugambwe wacu [w’Abarepubulika])
 Trump yabandanije kandi yerekana ko ashobora gusubira kwitoreza ikibanza c’umukuru w’igihugu mu 2024, abwira abatora ko boguma babanze amatwi mu myiyamamazo yiwe yo kuro uno wa mbere i Ohio
 Amatora ngereranyo yerekana ko aba-Democrats bashobora gutakaza ubwiganze mu nama nshingamateka
 Ubwiganze mu nama nkenguzamateka bushobora kuzovana n’ibizova mu matora muri Pennsylvania, Georgia na Nevada, aho impande zompi zibangabanganywe cane
 Abantu barenga imiriyoni 40 baramaze gutora gushika ubu muri ya matora y’imbere y’umusi w’amatora, nk’uko abahinga babivuga, igitigiri gisumvye ic’abari batoye imbere y’igihe mu matora ya 2018

A﻿nne Ngugi B﻿BC Swahili I﻿bintu vyifashe nabi mu ruhongore kama rw'ibikoko rwa Amboseli mu bumanuko bwa Kenya, aho kubera uruzuba ibikoko biguma bipfa bivuye kukubura ivyo birya
 I﻿biziga vy'ibikoko vyo mw'ishamba biboneka hirya no hino muri iryo shamba birerekana amapfa yatewe n'iryo zuba
 I﻿vyo bikoko bipfa, birababaza abantu benshi mu gihe umunuko wavyo uguma wibutsa abantu ko urupfu ari ikintu gisigaye gisanzwe
 A﻿bamenyeshamakuru ba BBC bariboneye n'amaso yabo ingene inzovu yoba ifise nk'imyaka 40 iriko irasandaba
 N﻿k'uko abahaba babivuga, ngo ivyo bishika misi yose kandi ntibigira ingaruka gusa ku bikoko, hari n'ingaruka zo ku bantu baba mu micungararo y'urwo ruhongore
 A﻿bo bantu bavuga ko basanzwe bakunda cane ivyo bikoko, cane cane inzovu, kubibona rero biriko birapfa bibatera ububabare butagira uko bungana
 U﻿mwe mubacungera urwo ruhongore kama agira ati:"Turababaye cane, hari umugani baca mu rurimi rw'iki masai ko ubonye ibikoko binini  nk'akarorero inzovu biriko birapfa, bisigura ko ibintu biba bimeze nabi cane
" B﻿iragoye cane ko umuntu atwara imodoka n'aho coba ari ikilometero kimwe atarabona ibiziga aha canke hariya muri iryo shamba
 Haraboneka ibiziga vy'ibikoko bitandukanye
 N﻿'aho ivyo bikoko biriko birapfa, ingenzi zirabandanya kuza ari nyinshi muri urwo ruhongore kama, nta n'ikintu kihari kibabuza kwinjira n'imodoka kuraba ibikoko bakunda, kuko vyinshi biba vyinyegeje mu duce bikunze kubamwo
 B﻿arabandanya kwegeranya ibiharuro vy'ibikoko vyapfuye bizize uruzuba ruri mu bice bimwe bimwe vya Kenya
