 U﻿mushikiranganji w'ibidukikije n'ingenzi wa Kenya Penina Malonza, aherutse kuvuga ko igihugu kimaze gutakaza inzovu 205 muri uyu mwaka gusa bivuye ku ruzuba rwinshi rwadutse muri ico gihugu co mu buseruko bwa Afrika
 N﻿k'uko bivugwa n'uwo mushikiranganji, ahantu haba ibikoko ibihumbi n'ibihumbi, hatakirangwa ivyatsi kubera uruzuba, vyarahapfiriye kubera kubura amazi n'uburagiro
 A﻿vuga ko mu bikoko bimaze gupfa harimwo ingamiya zirenga amajana atanu, imparage zababa amajana ane hamwe n'imbogo
