 Perezida Zelensky avuga ko abanyagihugu imiriyoni 4
5 ata muyagankuba bafise inyuma y’ibitero vy’Uburusiya ku bigo vy’amasoko ntanganguvu
 Mu ndwi nkeya ziheze, Uburusiya bwakoze ibitero bikomeye vya misire na za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) ku bigo vy’umuyagankuba
 Ibi bitero vyabaye mu gihe abategetsi bavuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zishobora kuva mu gisagara gikomeye ca Kherson kiri mu bumanuko bw’igihugu
 Inyuma yo gutakaza bikomeye ku rubuga rw’intambara, Uburusiya bwaciye bwongereza ibitero  ku bigo vy’umuyagankuba mu bisagara biri kure y’urubuga rw’intambara
 Mu kwezi guheze kwonyene, ica gatatu c’ibigo vy’umuyagankuba bivugwa ko vyasambuwe, nk’uko Perezida Zelensky abitangaza
 Vyabaye ngombwa ko reta ya Ukraine isaba abanyagihugu kugerageza gukoresha umuyagankuba mukemuke kuri iyo mvo
 Nijoro ku wa kane mw’ijambo yama ashikiriza buri ijoro, Perezida Zelensky  yavuze ati: "Muri iri joro, abanyagihugu bababa imiriyoni 4,5 nta muyagankuba bafise”
 Avuga ko kubona Uburusiya buhindukirira gutera ibigo ntanganguvu ari ikimenyetso “c’inguvu zabuheranye” mu gihe ingabo zabwo zananiwe no gutera intambwe ikomeye ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Ati: "Kuba Uburusiya bwahisemwo iterabwoba rishingiye ku masoko ntanganguvu vyerekana ko umwansi yatakaje inguvu
 "Ntibashobora gutsinda Ukraine ku rubuga rw’intambara, rero ni co gituma bagerageza guca intege abanyagihugu bacu muri ubu buryo”
 Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Uburusiya bwemeje ko buriko buratera ibigo ntanganguvu vya Ukraine
 Ibirego vya Zelensky ku Burusiya bije mu gihe hari amakuru avuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya ziriko zirava mu gisagara zari zarigaruriye ca Kherson, ikimenyetso c’uko Uburusiya buriko burasubira inyuma
 Umutegetsi yashizweho n’Uburusiya mu ntara ya Kherson, Kirill Stremousov, yabwiye ibinyamakuru vy’Uburusiya ko Moscou “ishobora” gukura ngabo zayo muri ako karere
 Hanyuma kandi nk’uko umutegetsi umwe wo mu Burengero, ariko atashatse ko izina ryiwe rimenyekana, abivuga, intwazangabo hafi zose z’Uburusiya zirongoye urugamba zamaze kuva muri ico gisagara
 Hakugerageza kugumana iki gisagara, bavuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya, mu buryo bwo kwivuna, ziriko ziriyegeranya hakurya y’uruzi Dnipro, mu gikorwa kinini co kwubaka ibirindiro vyo kwivuna umwansi neza mu bumanuko n’ubuseruko bwa Ukraine imbere y’umuzo w’urushana
 Biragoye kumenya neza na neza ibiriko birabera muri ico gisagara, ariko uyo mutegetsi avuga ko ingabo ziherutse kwinjizwa muri wa mugambi wo kwinjiza ngabo z’integabizoza mu gisirikare c’Uburusiya zarungitswe muri ico gisagara kugira ngo zihagararire igikorwa ca nyuma co kuva ku birindiro biramutse bishitse
 Hejuru y’ivyo, umunyamakuru wa BBC Paul Adams amenyesha ko amabanki avugwa ko yanyazwe urukombamazi co kimwe n’amazu ndangamurage
 Abategetsi bashizweho n’Uburusiya nabo bamaze amayinga atari make bahungisha abasivire ibihumbi n’ibihumbi muri ako karere
 Umunyamabanga wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ajejwe kwivuna abansi Lloyd Austin avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zifise “ubushobozi” bwo kubohoza ico gisagara co mu bumanuko
 Ariko Ukraine ivuga ko ibandanya irwana muri ako karere kandi ko ibandanya yicungereye yibaza ko Uburusiya buriko butega umutego ingabo za Ukraine
 Igihe Uburusiya bwigarurira Kherson – igisagara gikomeye – mu kwa gatatu, vyabonetse ko ari imwe mu ntambwe zikomeye Moscou yari iteye muri iyo ntambara
 Ariko igitero co kwivuna muri ako karere kimaze ukwezi kurenga cerekana ko Uburusiya ari ngombwa ko bwihweza gushasha intumbero z’urugamba

N﻿a Patrick Jackson & Merlyn Thomas BBC News, London Ikoraniro ry’inama nshingamateka y’Ubufaransa ryahagaritswe inyuma y’aho umushingamateka wo ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku vyiyumviro bikaze vyo gushira imbere inyungu z’igihugu (Far-right/ Extrême droite) avugirije induru avuga ngo “ni basubire iwabo muri Afrika”, hari mu gihe mugenziwe w’umwirabure yavuga ibijanye n’abimukira
 Mu nyuma Grégoire de Fournas, umunywanyi w’umugambwe Rassemblement National (RN)  yahavuye avuga ko amajambo yiwe atari ayo kwifatira Carlos Martens Bilongo ubwiwe, ariko ko yari ayo kwiyamiriza abimukira bagerageza kwinjira i Bulaya baciye mu kiyaga
 Bilongo yavuze ko yavukiye mu Bufaransa kandi ko ayo majambo “ateye isoni”
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Elisabeth Borne avuga ati "amacakubiri nta kibanza afise "
 Ibiro vy’inama nshingamateka bishobora gukorana kuri uno wa gatanu kugira ngo “bifate ibihano bikenewe”, nk’uko umunyaporitike yigenga yabibwiye abanyamakuru
 Bilongo yari amaze igihe atera akamo reta ku bijanye n’igisabo c’ishirahamwe ritegamiye reta SOS Méditerranée risaba ko horonderwa ikibanza co gushikizamwo abimukira 234 baherutse kurokorwa mu kiyaga mu misi iheze
 Igihe umushingamateka de Fournas yavuga aya majambo, umukuru w’inama nshingamateka, Yael Braun-Pivet, yaciye arondera kumenya uwari ahejeje kuvuga
 Niho, mu gihe abashingamateka biha akaruru bavuga bati “Hanze! Hanze! Hanze!”, yaciye ahagarika inama, avuga ati: “Ibi ntibishoboka”
 Bilongo, umushingamateka wo mu mugambwe La France Insoumise (LFI), avuga ati: "Uno musi wagarutse kw’ibara ry’urukoba rwanje
 Navukiye mu Bufaransa, ndi umushingamateka w’umufaransa”
 De Fournas yagerageje kwisigura, avuga ko yashatse kuvuga “ubwato butwara abantu i Bulaya” ariko mu nyuma aza gusaba imbabazi Bilongo kubera “ukutumvikana” amajambo yiwe yateje n’umubabaro yoba yamuteye
 Umukuru w’umugambwe LFI Jean-Luc Mélenchon yanditse kuri Twitter ko amajambo y’uyo mushingamateka "arengeye urugero rwo kubabarirwa" kandi ko yategerezwa kwirukanwa mu nama nshingamateka
 Ikibazo c’abimukira caribonekeje cane mu gihe c’imyiyamamazo mu matora y’umukuru w’igihugu n’abashingamateka mu mugambwe RN uno mwaka, aho umukuru w’uyo mugambwe Marine Le Pen yemereye abanywanyi biwe ko hoba kamarampaka ku ngingo zo kugabanya abimukira mu gihe yoba umukuru w’igihugu
 Mu matora y’abashingamateka mu kwa gatandatu, uyu mugambwe wararwijije ibibanza incuro cumi mu nama nshingamateka, aho waronse intebe 89

Na Alex de Waal U﻿musesenguzi wa Africa Amakungu yarashimye amasezerano yemejwe na reta ya Ethiopia n'indongozi za Tigray yo kurangiza intambara mu buraruko bw'igihugu kandi huguruwe inzira y'imfashanyo ku bantu bari bugarijwe n'inzara, ariko haracari ibibazo vyo kumenya niba azorama
 Umunsi umwe inyuma y'amashi yo mu birori vyo gushira umukono ku masezerano  ku murwa mukuru wa Africa y'Epfo, Pretoria, urwamo rw'ibisasu biremereye  rwari rucumvikana mu misozi ya Tigryay
 Ayo masezerano ahuye ahanini n'ivyashaka gushikwako n'umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Ethiopia, Abiy Ahmed, igihe yatanguza ico yise "igikorwa co kwubahiriza amategeko" mu kurwanya umugambwe watwara iyo ntara - Tigray People's Liberation Front (TPLF)- haraheze imyaka ibiri, umunsi ku wundi
 Hazoba igikorwa co kwaka ibigwanisho abagwanyi ba Tigray hisunzwe  uko vyumvikanyeko
 Aho Abiy afitiye ico asumbije uruhande bari bahanganye, n'uko ayo masezerano bayagiranye na TPLF, batayagiranye na reta ya Tigray, nk'uko abanya-Tigray bari bavyifuje
 Ntiyemera amatora yabaye muri Tigray mu 2020 agatsindwa na TPLF, kandi ategekanya amatora mashasha
 Ariko kandi, reta mpuzantara yari yashatse ko TPLF ishira amaboko hejuru ata kindi kirenze aho
 Ariko ivyo ntiyabishitseko
 Yemeye guheba kwita TPLF ishirahamwe ry'iterabwoba, hanyuma ije mu biganiro vy'ingene intara ya Tigray yotwarwa
 Ayo masezerano avuga ko impande zomnpi zokwubahiriza ingene ibwirizwa nshingiro mpuzantara risanzwe ryubatse
 Iryo ririmwo ingingo z'uko  ibibazo vy'intara nk'uburengero bwa Tigray bw'isi imera cane - bwigaruriwe n'intara ya Amhara bihana urubibe mu ndwi za mbee z'intambara - bikemurwa biciye mu buryo bw'ibwirizwa shingiro
 \nNtavuga niba  ubutegetsi bwa Tigray - n'abarimyi amatongo yabo - bazobanza kugaruka
 Ikigabane cerekeye akaga kugarije abantu cugurura inzira yo kurangiza inzara no kubuza abantu gushikira ivya nkenerwa vyatumye hapfaa abantu bashika umuriyoni umwe
 Aho harimwo kumbure 10% y'abanya-Tigray bose hamwe baharurwa mu miriyoni 6, hisunzwe ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahinga bo mu Bubirigi
 Inyuma y'imyaka ibiri yo kwugarana iyo ntara no kuyicisha inzara, no kuyigumizako igitutu ca gisirikare c'ingabo za Ethiopia zifatanije n'iza Eritrea, hakajako n'iz'intara ya Amhara, indongozi za Tigray zemeye guheba vyinshi cane
 Igiharuro cabo gishobora kuba cabaye ico kwemera ko ubuzima bw'abanya-Tigray bwari bugeramiwe
 Abantu barenga umuriyoni barataye izabo kuva intanbara isubiye kwaduka muri Myandagaro(ukwezi kw'umunani), ntibashobora gusarura ivyo barimye
 Abantu bariko baricwa n'indwara zishobora kuvurwa kuko ibitaro ata miti y'ibanze bigisigaranye nka insuline na antibiotique
 \nKandi nta kimenyetso ko ivyo biriko birarangira
 Ku bantu baharurwa muri za miriyoni bamaze igihe bataronka ivyo kurya, imiti n'ibindi vya nkenerwa vy'ibanze, imfashanyo ikenewe cane ntikwiye kumara uwundi munsi itarashika
 Hari ibibazo bitararonka inyishu
 Bitatu muri vyo birahambaye cane
 Ubwa mbere ni Eritrea
 Ku bw'abajejwe imigenderanire b'ibihugu vy'iburengerazuba, ibitero vya gisirikare vyashenye ukwivuna kw'abanya-Tigray, n'ubufatanye bw'ingabo za Eritrea na Ethiopia vyagabwe biva muri Asmara
 Eritrea ntivugwa mw'izina muri ayo masezerano
 Ariko iyo nyandiko irimwo ingingo yo kurangiza "gukorana n'ingabo zo hanze ziterekwa uruhande rumwe canke urundi", bishobora kuba bishaka kuvuga Eritrea
 Hari benshi bashobora kutizera ko reta ifise uburyo bwo kubishira mu ngiro
 Umukuru wa Eritrea Isaias Afewerki ntarimwo mu bemeje ayo masezerano kandi afise uburyo bwo kubandanya iyo ntambara ataravye amasezerano ayari yo yose yashitsweko na Abiy
 Ikibazo ca kabiri ni ukugenzura n'uguhinyuza
 Ayo masezerano ni intsinzi ya reta ya Ethiopia mu ruyeri rwayo rwo kugumiza amakungu kure
 Urwego rwo gucungera, guhinyuza no kwubahiriza ishirwa mu ngiro ry'ayo masezerano rugizwe n'umugwi muto cane - w'abantu batarenze 10- baha icegeranyo umugwi w'ishirahamwe rya Afrika urongowe n'uwahoze ari umukuru wa Nigeria Olusegun Obasanjo
 Kandi, igikorwa ca  Obasanjo yagihawe n'umukuru w'urwego rutwara ishirahamwe rya Afrika Mousa Faki, ntiyagihawe n'urwego rw'iryo shirahamwe rujejwe amahoro n'umutekano
 ONU nta kibanza ifisemwo na gato
 Kwihweza ibijanye no kurenga ku masezerano no gutorera inyishu amatati bizoba biri mw'ibanga ry'abagabo babiri - Obasanjo na Faki - uburyo budasanzwe bwo kugenzura, umuntu avyoroheje
 Ubundi vyari bimenyerewe ko amasezerano y'amahoro yo ku rwego rwo hejuru ahagarikirwa n'abafatanyabikorwa mpuzamakungu
 Ingene vyagenze ubu, Ishirahamwe rya Afrika ryemereye ONU, Amerika, n'urwergo rwo muri Afrika y'Ubuseruko Igad nk'abarorerezi gusa, ariko nta n'umwe yashize umukono kuri ayo masezerano
 Ishirahamwe rya Buraya ryarankiwe kuba indorerezi, n'ubwo ariryo rya mbere riha amafaranga menshi ishirahamwe rya Afrika
 Ariko Ethiopia n'ishirahamwe rya Afrika bizokenera gushigikirwa n'amakungu - na cane cane ko Ethiopia ikeneye cane imfashanyo iva hanze
 Ikibazo ca gatatu ni ubutungane n'ukubazwa ivyo wakoze
 Amasezerano ategekanya ko reta ya Ethiopia ishiraho "poritike y'ubutungane bw'inyuma y'intambara", ariko ntaco avuga ku matohoza mpuzamakungu, nk'akarorero ayo urwego rwa ONU rujejwe agateka ka zina muntu canke urwego rw'ishirahamwe rya Afrika rujejwe agateka ka zina muntu
 Obasanjo yavuze ko gushira umukono ku masezerano ari intambwe imwe, ko kuyashira mu ngiro kizoba igikorwa kigoye gusumba
 Amahoro no kurangiza amahano n'inzara muri Tigray hamwe no kugarukana amaragamo muri Ethiopia ahanini bihagaze ku gushaka kwa reta mpuzantara
 Intango ya mbere izoba ko yemera kuja hamwe na TPLF kugira basohorere hamwe  amatangazo yo kwiyemeza kurangiza "propagande iterakwa urundi ruhande, hamwe n'amajambo y'urwanko"
 Abanya-Tigray mu gihugu no hanze ntibakiriye neza ayo masezerano
\nBirashoboka ko bamwe mu bategetsi b'ingabo bohitamwo kubandanya intambara yo mu tugwi duto duto aho kwemera ivyo babona nk'amasezerano y'akamaramaza
 Benshi mu makungu bafata ko Abiy ata gatimatare afise, kandi ko azogaruka mu nzira y'mahoro, demokrasi n'amaragamo hamwe yohabwa amahirwe
 Abandi bafise amakenga ko icigwa Abiy, Isaias n'abandi bakuyemwo ari igihushane c'ivyo - ko inguvu z'ikirenga, kwicisha inzara no kubuza  ko hamenyekana amakuru ari ikigwanisho nyaco mu gushika ku ntego zabo
 Abanya-Ethiopia bizeye ko bene ivyo bigwanisho bitazokoreshwa mu gutorera inyishu ibindi bibazo vya poritike, harimwo n'ubugarariji bubandanya mu ntara ya Oromia
 Ayo masezerano ashingiye ku kwizera ko Abiy  azovana Ethiopia muri ako kaga
 Ikimenyetso ca mbere cari ukwizera ko ibigwanisho vyari guca binuma ku wa kane
 Ivyo ntivyabaye
 Ahubwo uwo munsi waranzwe n'intambaraa ikomeye, irimwo ibitero bikomeye vy'ingabo za Ethiopia na Eritrea ku nzasiro zitatu, nk'uko amasoko abivuga
 Abanya-Tigray barihagazeko kandi bivugwa ko batatakaje ibirindiro
 Akamaro k'ishirahamwe rya Afrika n'abarorerezi mpuzamakungu muri ivyo biganiro -ONU, US na Igad- kazobonekera mu gutururuza abarenga ku masezerano ku mpande zose
 Alex de Waal ni umuyobozi nshi ngwabikorwa mu kigo World Peace Foundation c'igisata citwa Fletcher c'amategeko n'ivyigwa vy'imigenderanire ( diplomacie)  kuri kaminuza ya Tufts muri US

Itangazo ry'ubushikiranganji bw'ubutungane risaba abacamanza n'abashikirizamanza kutihutira gupfunga abantu bagirizwa ivyaha bito bito kuko batwara uburyo bwinshi reta
 D﻿omina Banyankimbona arongoye ubwo bushikiranganji agira ati: "Abapfunzwe barindiriye gucirirwa urubanza batwara uburyo bwinshi reta kuko bakenera uburaro, gufungura no kuvurwa
 "﻿Aho ni mu gihe baba bafise inguvu zo gukora kandi bagashobora guterera agacumu k'ubumwe mw'iterambere ry'igihugu
" I﻿shirahamwe riharanira agateka k'abanyororo, Ntabariza, rivuga ko gushika ubu abanyororo bari mu Burundi barenga ibihumbi 13 mu gihe hateguwe ibibanza birenga gato ibihumbi bine
 A﻿bakunze kwisanga mw'ibohero bidakwiriye ngo n'abantu baba bafitiye amadeni abandi, canke abakora ubusuma bwo ku ruyeri
 I﻿ryo tangazo ribandanya rivuga ko babandanya gupfungwa kandi reta yaramaze gutanga intumbero y'ingene bohanwa
 M﻿u gukora ivyo ngo ntibaba bafashije n'uwakorewe icaha
 R﻿igira riti: "Iyo abakoze icaha gito bapfunzwe, uwagikorewe nta co yunguka kuko nyene gukora icaha ntashobora kuronka ikimwinjiriza amahera kugira ashobore kumuriha
" R﻿yongerako ko "mukwiye kwiyumvira mukirinda gupfunga abantu bagirizwa ivyaha bito mukananyarutsa imanza z'abapfunzwe
 Ati: "﻿Korana n'abakorewe icaha, murondere ivyo ababikoze batunze mubategeke gutanga ingwati yerekana ko bemera kuriha
" M﻿w'ishirahamwe Ntabariza riharanira agateka k'abanyororo barashima ako kamo k'ubushikiranganji bw'ubutungane kuko ngo abapfunzwe batategerezwa kuba bari mw'ibohero ni benshi
 J﻿ean Marie Nshimirimana aserukira iryo shirahamwe imbere y'amategeko avuga ko uretse abapfungwa batakoze ivyaha bikomeye, hariho iyindi migwi y'abanyororo ituma igitigiri cabo kitagabanuka
 A﻿ha avuga nk'abanyororo bahejeje igipfungo cabo ariko bakabandanya bapfunzwe kubera bananiwe kuriha indishi z'akababaro canke ivyo bivye, ivyo bita "umunyororo w'agatsindikiro"
 H﻿ari kandi abarangiza umunyororo ariko bagaca baguma bapfunzwe n'ayandi makosa bakoreye mw'ibohero
 J﻿ean Marie Nshimirimana avuga ko icoza kigabanya igitigiri c'abanyororo ari ugutangura gushira mu bikorwa itegeko ritegekanya ibikorwa nsimburagifungo
 A﻿gira ati: "Nihatangure ibikorwa nsimburagifungo ku buryo nk'akarorero uwakoze icaha akora imisi ibiri muhira iwe, iyindi itatu akaja gukorera uwo yagikoreye kugira amurihe
 "﻿Canke bamuhe ibindi bikorwa akora biteza imbere igihugu mw'iterambere hakumugumiza mw'ibohero aho afungura, akoresha amazi akanahabwa uburaro vyose bivuye mu nguvu za reta
" I﻿shirahamwe Ntabariza rivuga ko mu makomine ivyo gupfunga abantu bakoze ivyaha bibayabaye biriko biragabanuka, ariko ngo biracibonekeza mu ma "PJ" (Police judiciaire)
 A﻿handi bigwiriye ngo ni mu ntara zitarimwo amabohero, kubera kubura uburyo bwo kwiyunguruza, abagirizwa ivyaha bamara igihe kirekire bapfungiwe mu gipolisi batarashikanwa mw'ibohero

Korea ya Ruguru yarashe igisasu ca misire cambukiranya imigabane, kizwi mu mpfunyapfunyo na ICBM (Intercontinental ballistic missile/ Missile balistique intercontinental), gishobora gutera umwansi yoba ari ku rundi ruhande rw’isi, nk’uko abategetsi ba Korea y’Epfo babitangaza
 Igerageza ry’iki gisasu ca ICBM kuri Pyongyang (umugwa mukuru wa Korea ya Rugugu) rigize indwi muri uno mwaka, rikaba ribaye mu gihe hari impungenge ko vuba igerageza ikirwanisho ca nikleyeri
 Ribaye kandi mu gihe Korea zompi zarashe ibisasu vya misire vyatumye icuka kibi kihasanzwe cunyuka
 Uku kurasa ibi bisasu bahanahana kwatumye Korea ya Ruguru irekura igitigiri ca mbere kinini c’ibisasu vya misire ku musi umwe
 Korea ya Ruguru igerageje ibisasu vyinshi mu gihe Amerika na Korea y’Epfo biri mu myimenyerezo rusangi minini yo mu kirere itari bwigere ibaho, imyimenyerezo Pyongyang yaneguye bikomeye ikayifata ko ari “agasotoro”
 Kuri uno wa kane, Korea ya Ruguru yarekuye igisasu ca misire kiraswa kure hafi y’isaha imwe n’iminota 40 (7:40) zo mu gatondo mu masaha yo muri ico gihugu, nk’uko itangazo rusangi ry’abakuru ba gisirikare ba Korea y’Epfo ribivuga
 Isoko rivyemeza ryabwiye BBC ko cari igisasu ca ICBM
 Cashitse ku ntera y’ibirometero 760 kiguruka gushika ku birometero 1
920 uja hejuru
 Ariko gisa n’icananiwe kikiri mu nzira, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Yonhap risubiramwo amasoko yaryo
 Pyongyang yararekuye kandi ibisasu vya misire biraswa ku ntera ya hafi
 Ibi bikorwa vyo kurasa za misire vyatumye muri kano gatondo ko ku wa kane reta y’Ubuyapani isohora itangazo ryo kugabisha, ibisanzwe bishika gake, isaba abanyagihugu bo mu turere tumwe tumwe  two mu buraruko kuguma mu mazu
 Mu ntango, Tokyo yavuze ko ico gisasu caciye hejuru y’Ubuyapani, ariko mu nyuma umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi Yasukazu Hamada akaba yavuze ko kitarenze “amazinga y’Ubuyapani, ariko cazimanganiye hejuru y’inyanja y’Ubuyapani”
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere  Fumio Kishida ariyamiriza ibikorwa vya Korea ya Ruguru vyo “kubandanya irekura ibisasu vya misire”, akavuga ko ari “akaga”
 Hagati aho, icegera c’umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire wa Korea y’Epfo Cho Hyun-dong hamwe n’icegera n’umunyamabanga wa Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire Wendy Sherman bavuze ko ibi bikorwa vyo kugerageza ibi bisasu "bibabaje kandi bikaba ivy’ubupfamutima”
 Ibi bibaye haciye ukwezi kumwe gusa Korea ya Ruguru irekuye igisasu ca misire kiraswa kure kigaca hejuru y’Ubuyapani – rikaba ryari irya mbere ikoze ivyo mu myaka itanu
 Korea ya Ruguru imaze kurekura igitigiri c’ibisasu vya misire ca mbere kinini muri uno mwaka mu gihe icuka kibi kibandanya ciyongera
 N’aho yafatiwe ibihano vyamugaje ubutunzi bwayo, Pyongyang yaragerageje ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri incuro zitandatu hagati ya 2006 na 2017 ikaba izwi ko iriko itegura igerageza rigira indwi
 Ibandanya ikomeza ubushobozi bwayo bwa gisirikare – ihonyanze ivyemezo vy’Inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano kw’isi – mu ntumbero yo gutera ubwoba ibihugu bibanyi ndetse mbere igire n’ubushobozi bwo gutera ubutaka bwa Amerika
