Ishami ryo mu Bwongereza rya kompanyi y’igihangange mu bitoro no  kwimba ubutare canke amabuye y’agaciro, Glencore, ryategetswe kuriha  miriyoni zirenga amajana atatu z’ama dorari (miriyaridi zirenga 600 mu mafaranga y’Uburundi) kubera amafaranga ryapfumbatishije abategetsi bo muri Afrika kugira rironke ibitoro
 Iyo kompnayi yahaye miriyoni 26 z’ama dorari, ibicishije ku bantu ituma n’abakozi bayo,  abategetsi bo mu bigo vy’ibitoro bitayunguruye muri Nigeria, Cameroun, na Cote d’Ivoire hagati ya 2011 na 2016
 Abashikirizamanza bavuze ko abakozi ba Glencore Energy UK  n’abandi bantu yatuma bakoresheje indege z’abantu ku giti cabo (jet prives)  kugira bajane ayo mafaranga yo gutanga ibiturire
 Glencore Energy UK mu kwezi kwa Ruheshi (kwa gatandatu) yemeye ivyaha indwi vy’ibiturire
 Yeciriwe kuriha ihadabu rya miriyoni zirenga 205 z’ama dorari n’umucamanza Peter Fraser wo muri sentare ya Crown Court ya Southwark, uwo mucamanza  yongera yemeza ko Glencore inyagwa izindi zishika hafi 105 z’ama dorari nyene
 Hamwe n’ivyo vyaha vyo gupfumbatisha, iyo kompanyi yemeye ivyaha yagirizwa vyo  kutabuza abakozi bayo gukoresha ipfumbatsisha (bribery) kugira baronke amasezerano (contrats)  y’ibitoro muri Guinee Equatoriale na Sudan y’Epfo
 Glencore, yashinzwe mu 1974, n’imwe mu ma kompanyi akomeye cane kw’isi mu bicuruzwa kama (comodity trader) hamwe no mu kwimba ibitoro, ubutare n’amabuye y’agaciro
 Amashami yayo akorera mu bihugu birenga 35, ariko ibiro vya Glencore i Londres bikorera cane cane mu bitoro, igisata cayo kimwe kikaba kijejwe Afrika y’uburengero
 Ivyo  birego vyo gupfumbatisha bivuga ko ico iyo kompanyi  yashaka kwari uko  abategetsi “badakora neza ivyo bajejwe, canke kubahemba kuba babigenjeje uko, mu guha Glencore Energy UK  kandi itari ibikwiye ibitoro  bitayunguruye”
 Mu 2018, ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane bwa Amerika bwatanguje amatohoza ku bijanye n’ingene Glencore yubahiriza amategeko ya Amerika yerekeye amafaranga y’inkomoko mbi n’ibiturire ku kiringo co kuva mu 2007
 Yari yerekeye ibikorwa vy’iyo kompanyi muri Nigeria, Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo na Venezuela
 Mu nyuma urwego rw’Ubwongereza rujejwe ivyaha vy’amanyanga bikomeye (Serious Fraud Office, SFO) narwo rwaciye rukurikira mu 2009, rutohoza kuri rimwe mu mashami ya Glencore ku “bishobora kuba ipfumbatisha”  muri Afrika
 SFO imbere y’aho yari yavuze ko amatohoza yayo yari yashize ahagaragara “gupfumbatisha hamwe n’ibiturire bigamije inyungu”
 Clare Montgomery, aserukira Glencore, yavuze ati: “Kompanyi iricuza yivuye inyuma ikibi catewe n’ivyo vyaha kandi iremera ko ikibi cakozwe, haba ku rugero rw’igihugu canke ku rugero rw’abanyagihugu muri ivyo bihugu vyo muri Afrika vyabayemwo, hamwe n’ico vyononeye abandi
” Umucamanza Fraser yavuze  igihe yariko arasoma urwo rubanza ko Glencore yakoze impinduka mu buryo yigenza ubu ikaba isa n’ikompanyi itandukanye n’iyo igihe ivyo vyaha vyakorwa”
 Mu kwezi kwa Rusama (5) , iyo kompanyi yemeye umwumvikano w’amafaranga angana na miriyaridi 1
1 z’ama dorari muri Amerika  bivuye ku ngendo  yayo yo gupfumbatisha mu bihugu indwi mu kiringo c’imyaka 10
 Ivyo vyari vyerekeye ibikorwa vy’ico gihangange muri Nigeria , RD Congo na Venezuela

Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zasubiye kwagiriza Korea ya Ruguru ko irungikira Uburusiya ibirwanisho mu ntambara yabwo na Ukraine
 Imboneshakure CNN isubiramwo amakuru y’igendereza rya Amerika yerekana ko Korea ya Ruguru ifasha Uburusiya mu ntambara yabwo muri Ukraine, mu kurungika vya muzinga itavuze aho bigiye
 Aya makuru agiye gusohoka amezi abiri inyuma y’aho inzego zijejwe igendereza za Amerika zitanguriye kwerekana ko Uburusiya bushobora kuba bugurira amabombe na za misire muri Korea ya Ruguru, nk’uko aya makuru abivuga
 John Kirby, umuvugizi w’inama nkuru y’igihugu ijejwe umutekano, yabwiye CNN ati: “Mu kw’icenda, Korea ya Ruguru yarahakanye ku mugaragaro ko ata mugambi ifise wo kurungikira amasasu Uburusiya
 “Ariko aho nyene, igashaka kwerekana ko ivyo birwanisho birungitswe mu burasirazuba bwo hagati canke muri Afrika y’Uburaruko”
 Abategetsi ntibarashobora guha CNN icemezo na kimwe c’ivyo bavuga, kandi n’inzego zijejwe igendereza ntizishira ahabona igitigiri c’ibirwanisho bimaze gutangwa canke ingene ibi bihugu vyarihanye mu masezerano yavyo
 Hagati aho, abanyamerika babona ko ibi birwanisho bitangwa na Korea ya Ruguru, biri kumwe na za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) ziva muri Irani, vyerekana ko inyuma y’amezi umunani y’intambara, ububiko bw’Uburusiya bw’ibirwanisho vyemewe gukoreshwa butanguye guhererwa, nk’uko abavyandika babivuga
 Haraheze amayinga yababa abiri umukuru w’igendereza rya Amerika Euryl Haynes avuze ko “igenzurwa ry’ibidandazwa bishorwa hanze ririko rihatira Uburusiya guhindukirira ibihugu nka Irani na Korea ya Ruguru kugira buronke za drones, ibisasu vya muzinga hamwe n’ibisasu vya misire”
 Ku ruhande rwiwe, Kirby yavuze ejo ku wa gatatu ko imfashanyo Irani na Korea ya Ruguru biha Uburusiya zidashobora guhindura inzira y’iyi ntambara
 Gusa, ibi birwanisho burungikirwa bishobora kubufasha kubandanya intambara yo gukoresha vya muzinga ku rugamba
 "Tuzobandanya dukurikiranira hagufi ingene ibi birwanisho bitangwa”, niko avuga, agashimangira ko Uburusiya buriko bugerageza kurondera gufatwa mu mugongo n’ibihugu nka Korea ya Ruguru na Irani mu ntumbero yo kubandanya intambara kuri Ukraine “mu gihe uburyo buriko bubuherana ibihano mpuzamakungu na vyo bikora akazi kavyo”
 Imbere y’aha, ibinyamakuru vy’Uburengero vyatangaje ko Irani yariko irategura kurungikira Uburusiya ibindi birwanisho hafi 1
000, harimwo ibisasu vya misire biraswa ku ntera ngufi hamwe na drones zo gukora ibitero
 Isubiramwo abategetsi bo mu Burengero, CNN ivuga iti: "Ubu buzoba bubaye ubwa mbere Irani irungikiye Uburusiya misire zidahusha, bigashobora guha akoyoko Kremlin ku rugamba”
 Nk’uko abategetsi babivuga, mu birwanisho Irani iherutse kurungikira Uburusiya harimwo drones zababa 450 Uburusiya bumaze gukoresha mu bitero muri Ukraine

