Uburusiya  bwagavye ibitero vyinshi vya misire muri Ukraine, harimwo no ku murwa mukuru  Kyiv bituma amatara  n’amazi bicika, nk’uko bivugwa n’abategetsi ba Ukraine
 Ku murwa mukuru Kyiv haturikiye nibura bibiri
 Umwe mu bahaba yabwiye BBC ko akarere abamwo katagira umuyagankuba
 Mu gisagara ca Kharkiv co mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko, ibikorwa-remezo bihambaye vyagemwe, nk’uko abategetsi baho babivuga
 Ivyo bibaye inyuma y’aho Uburusiya bwagiririje Ukraine igitero ca drone ku bwato bwabwo mu Kiyaga Cirabura (Black Sea/Mer Noire) muri Crimea
 Ku wa  mbere mu gitondo, ibitero vya misire vyavuzwe kandi mu  ntara yo hagati na hagati ya Vinnytsia, co kimwe co no muri  Dnipropetrovsk na Zaporizhzhia mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko, hamwe na Lviv muri Ukraine y’uburengero
 Hari n’ivyononekaye ku rugomero rw’amatara rwa Dnipro  i Zaporizhzhia
 Muri Kyiv, ivyuma bitanga umuriro ku mazu  350
000 vyononywe, ubu abahinga bakaba bariko barakora uko bashoboye kugira bisubire gukora
 Ntivyashotse bimenyekna niba hari abapfuye canke ngo bakomereke
 Ababa mu ntara zatewe basabwe kuguma  aho bikinga, mu gihe hari ubwoba ko ibindi bitero bishobora gukurikira
 Zimwe muri misire zakorowe, nk’uko abategetsi ba Ukraine babivuga
 Umushikranhganji wa Ukraine ajejwe imigenderanire Dmytro Kuleba yavuze ko “aho kurwana ku rugamba, Uburusiya burwanya abanyagihugu basanzwe”
 Hagati aho uwuserukira Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri Ukraine, Bridget Brink, yanditse kuri twitter ati: “Co kimwe na miriyoni z’abanya-Ukraine, abakozi ba ambasade yacu basubiye kurondetra aho bikinga mu gihe Uburusiya bukomeye ibitero bunyamaswa vyabwo vya misire ku banya-Ukraine  kugira batume haba imbeho n’umwijima mu gihe twimirije igihe c’ubukonje (hiver)
 Gushika ubu Uburusiya ntaco buravuga kuri ivyo bitero
 Ku wa gatandatu, ubwato bw’intambara bw’Uburusiya bwarononywe mu gisagara kiri ku kivuko ca Sevastopol mu gitero ca drone , nk’uko vyavuzwe n’ubushikiranganji bw’Uburusiya bujejwe kwivuna abansi
 Bwagirije kandi abahinga b’Ubwomngereza kuba bigishije abasirikare ba Ukraine mu nyuma nabo baca bakora ivyo bitero kuri Crimea, intara ya Ukraine yigaruriwe n’Uburusiya mu 2014
 Uburusiya nta vyemezo bwatanze vyo gushigikira ivyo buvuga
 Ukraine ntaco yavuze kuri ico kibazo, mu gihe Ubwongereza bwavuze ko Uburusia “bwarengeje mu  kuvuga ibinyoma”

Inama Nkuru yo kwivuna abansi (Conseil Supérieur de la Défense)  muri Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo isaba reta y’iki gihugu kwirukana uwuserukira Urwanda muri ico gihugu, Vincent Karega
 Mw’ikoraniro ry’abagize iyo Nama Nkuru yo kwivuna abansi yari irongowe na Perezida Félix Tshisekedi ejo ku wa gatandatu, basubiye kwagiriza Urwanda ko “rubandanya rwihisha inyuma y’umurwi w’iterabwoba wa M23 mu gutera Congo”, nk’uko biri mw’itangazo ryaraye risohowe na Patrick Muyaya, umuvugizi wa reta ya Congo
 Haraciye imisi intambara zibica bigacika hagati y’ingabo za Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo n’umuhari M23, reta ikagiriza Urwanda ko rufasha M23, ivyo reta y’Urwanda na M23 nyene bamirira kure
 Gushika ku wa gatanu, M23 ivugwa ko yari yamaze kwigarurira uturere hafi twose twa Busanza, Jomba, Bweza na Kisigari, hamwe n’ibigwati bimwe bimwe vy’akarere ka Rugari, kari ku birometero 30 mu buraruko bw’igisagara ca Goma
 Iri tangazo rivuga ko iyo nama yari iyo kwihweza ingene ibintu bimeze mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru imaze igihe “irangwamwo ibitero hamwe n’uturere tumwe tumwe twa Congo, muri teritware (Territoire) ya Rutshuru, twigaruriwe na M23 ifashwe mu mugongo n’Urwanda”, nk’uko biri muri iryo tangazo
 Rivuga riti: “Ku vyegeranyo biva ku rubuga, harimwo n’Ikigo Rusangi c’Ibikorwa vya gisirikare (Centre Conjoint des Opérations) gifise n’ama drones [za ndege zitagira abadereva] z’inderetsi, biraboneka muri ino misi, ko ingabo z’igisirikare c’Urwanda zinjira ku bwinshi gufasha umuhari w’iterabwoba wa M23 mu ntumbero yo gukora igitero gikomeye ku birindiro vy’ingabo za Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo”
 “Inama Nkuru yo Kwivuna abansi yibutsa ko iki gitero ca M23 gifashwe mu mugongo n’igisirikare c’Urwanda congeye guhonyanga ku ncuro yindi umugambi w’amahoro wa Nairobi na Luanda umaze amezi atari make”
 Hampande y’uko Urwanda rwagirizwa gufasha M23, iyo nama yagiriza abategetsi b’iki gihugu kibanyi “ubwibone n’agasuzuguro”, mu guhonyanga umugambi w’amahoro wa Nairobi na Luanda ndetse n’ibisabwa n’amakungu ko “ibikorwa vy’iterabwoba vya M23 hamwe n’imfashanyo yo hanze ironka” bihagarara
 “Rero, dufatiye kuri ivyo bihejeje gushikirizwa, Inama Nkuru yo kwivuna abansi isaba reta kwirukana, mu masaha 48 kuva abimenyeshejwe, nyakwubahwa Vincent Karega, umuserukizi w’Urwanda muri Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo”
 Iyo nama kandi isaba reta “gufatira Urwanda izindi ngingo zo kutinjira ku butaka bwa Congo”
 Itera akamo abanyagihug kwirinda “amajambo ayo ari yo yose, ubugizi bwa nabi canke inenwa vyokorerwa abanyagihugu bavuga ururimi rw’ikinyarwanda kugira ngo umwansi ntaronke inyendamuvano”, igasaba inzego zibijejwe ko zihagararira iki cipfuzo
 Reta y’Urwanda ntaco irashikiriza kuri ibi bisabwa n’Inama Nkuru ijejwe kwivuna abansi ya Congo, hamwe n’ivyo rubandanya rwagirizwa vyo gufasha M23
 Hagati aho, yaba reta, waba umuhari wa M23, bose bamye biyamiriza ivyo baregwa na reta ya Congo, ahubwo bakayagiriza ko ikorana n’umuhari w’inyeshamba FDLR urwanya reta y’Urwanda, hamwe n’interahamwe zagirizwa jenoside yo mu Rwanda, mu 1994
 Reta ya Congo ivuga ko ivyo yagirizwa n’Urwanda vyo gukorana na FDLR ari urwitwazo rwa leta y'ico gihugu kidafitiye ivyemezo rugituma ibandanya isotora Congo
 Lord (Tariq)Ahmad of Wimbledon, umushikiranganji wa reta y’Ubwongereza ajejwe Aziya y’epfo, uburasirazuba bwo hagati, ONU n’uburenganzira bwa muntu, akongera kaba n’intumwa idasanzwe y’umushikiranganji wa mbere mu kurwanya ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina,  amenyesha ko reta y’Ubwongereza yiyamiriza iyi ntambara n’ingene M23 igenda yigarurira uturere
 Mu butumwa yacishije ku rubuga rwa Twitter, Lord (Tariq)Ahmad avuga ati: “Imishamirano itegerezwa guhagarara
 Gufasha M23 bitegerezwa guhagarara
 Impande zompi zitegerezwa kuja mu biganiro”

N﻿a Bernd Debusmann Jr & Hugo Bachega BBC News, Washington  &  Kyiv Igabisha ry’aba Repubulika ko bashobora kugabanya imfashanyo ihabwa Ukraine mu gihe boramuka batsinze amatora bakiganzira inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka iriko yongereza akariro mu matora yimirije
 Ariko none, koko hari icohinduka
 Videwo yashizwe ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi n’ubushikiranganji bwa Ukraine bujejwe kwivuna abansi yerekana ikiboneka nka kimwe mu vyerekana ubushobozi bw’iki gihugu mu ntambara yaco n’Uburusiya
 Yerekana inguvu za roketi yakorewe muri Amerika irashwe mu kirere, ikurikiwe n’urubeya rw’umuriro rumukira mu kirere c’ijoro igihe yari igemye ico yari igenewe
 Iki kirwanisho, kizwi nka HIMARS (mu majambo yose High Mobility Artillery Rocket System), ni kimwe muri 18 gushika ubu Amerika imaze guha Ukraine
 Kiri mu mfashanyo nini cane ifise agaciro k’imiriyoni 52 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika, ikaba ingana incuro zibiri y’izindi mfashanyo zimaze gutangwa n’ibindi bihugu vyose biri hamwe
 Abahinga ba gisirikare hamwe na reta ya Ukraine bavuga ko iyi mfashanyo yabaye kirumara mu bikorwa vyabo
 Mark Cancian yahoze ari koroneri mu gisirikare ca Amerika akaba n’umuhinga mu bijanye no kwivuna abansi mu kigo Center for Strategic & International Studies avuga ati:  "Abanya-Ukraine baba barakubiswe iyo kitaba iki”
 Ariko rero izi mfashanyo zishobora guhura n’ikibazo
 Bamwe mu bashingamateka b’aba Repubulika baribaza akamaro kazo mu gihe Abanyamerika batorohewe n’iduga ry’ibiciro
 Mu ntango z’ukwa cumi, uwurongoye inkehwa mu nama nshingamateka Kevin McCarthy – akaba ari we mutegetsi ari ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ruhande rw’aba Repubulika mu nama nshingamateka  - avuga ko inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka zititeguye kwemerera Ukraine ibidashoboka
 Ubu,  umugambwe wiwe niwo uhabwa amahirwe yo kwiganzira inama nshingamateka ari nayo itegura ivyemezo vyose vy’amafaranga akoreshwa, nk’uko ibwirizwashingiro rya Amerika ribitegekanya
 Nk’umukuru w’inama nshingamateka, McCarthy  niwe azofata ingingo ku nteguro z’amategeko ashikanwa mu nama nshingamateka kugira ngo zemezwe canke zihakanwe
 N’abandi ba Repubulika bashikiriza amakenga nk’ayo nyene
 Mu kwa gatanu, nk’akarorero, umukenguzamateka wa Missouri Josh Hawley yavuze ko imfashanyo ya Ukraine idatangwa “mu nyungu za Amerika” kandi ko “ituma Ubulaya ata ruhara bugira”
 Aya majambo asa n’ayerekaye ukutumvikana kuri mu mugambwe, mu gihe uwahoze ari icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu Mike Pence yiyamiriza bikomeye abakorera Putin bama bazana ivyitwazo, hamwe n’abanywanyi b’umugambwe wiwe “bashobora kudutuma twitandukanya n’isi yose”
 Hampande y’uyo, umukuru w’abakenguzamateka b’aba Repubulika Mitch McConnell  asaba Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu wa Amerika) kwongerereza Ukraine imfashanyo, akavuga ko Amerika ikeneye “gukora gusumba igaha Ukraine ibikoresho ikeneye kugira ngo irwanye igitero c’Uburusiya”
 Igisumbirije, ni uko abarepubulika - 57 mu nama nshingamateka hamwe na 11 mu nama nkenguzamateka – ni bo bonyene batemeje imfashanyo yari igenewe Ukraine ifise agaciro k’imiriyoni 40 z’amadorari mu mpera z’urushana
 Amakenga abandanya yiyongera i Bulaya ku gishobora gushika
 Tobias Ellwood, umushingamateka w’Ubwongereza arongoye umurwi ujejwe kwivuna abansi mu nama nshingamateka, yabwiye ikinyamakuru Washington Post ati:  "Mu gihe Amerika yovanamwo akarenge, Putin yoca yikura mu menyo y’urupfu agashikira intsinzi”
 Ariko abategetsi ba Ukraine hamwe n’abihweza ibintu n’ibindi b’abanyamerika bavuga ko bidashoboka ko imfashanyo ihagarikwa ubwo nyene, uko ari ko kwose amatora yo mu kw’icumi na rimwe yogenda
 Avugana na BBC i Kyiv, umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi wa Ukraine Oleksii Reznikov avuga ko imibonano aherutse kugiriranira n’abashingamateka ba Amerika  - harimwo aba Democrats n’abaRepubulika -  yamuhaye icizere
 Ati: "Naronse ibimenyetso ko uwotsinda wese


impande zompi zobandanya zishigikira imfashanyo kuri Ukraine
 Ico ndacemera”
 John Herbst yari umuserukizi wa Amerika i Kyiv hagati ya  2003 na 2006, avuga ko McCarthy ashobora kugwa mu mutego wa poritike ku nyungu z’uruhande rw’abagendera ku vyiyuviro vya kera mu mugambwe wiwe
 Yabwiye BBC ati: "Nta nkeka ko ku ruhande rw’abanywanyi ba Trump, hari impungenge ku mfashanyo ihabwa Ukraine, mbere hakaba, n’aho boba ari bake muri bo, abatabona ryiza Ukraine, be n’abandi bubaha Uburusiya bwa Putin”
 Yongerako y’uko hari amahirwe ko urwo ruhande muri uyo mugambwe rushobora kugira inguvu mu nama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka inyuma y’amatora, ariko ic’uko ibi bishobora gutuma imfashanyo ihagarara, ni ikindi kibazo
 Aba Democrats bishura ku majambo ya McCarthy bashimangira ko bashigikiye Ukraine, ariko ntibabuze ababarwanya mu mugambwe wabo kuri ico kibazo
 Hari umurwi w’abaDemocrats vyabaye ngombwa ko basokora urwandiko rwabo rwasaba ko haba ibiganiro mu ntumbero yo kurangiza intambara muri Ukraine, inyuma yo kwagirizwa ko bariko basuzugura Perezida  Joe Biden
 Amatohoza yerekana ko abenshi bagishigikiye iyi ntambara ariko hari ibimenyetso ko ibitigiri bigenda bigabanuka uko intambara iba ndende
 Mu kwezi guheze, 20% vy’abanyamerika bavuze ko Amerika iriko iha Ukraine imfashanyo zirenze urugero, nk’uko bivugwa n’ikigo Pew Research, mu gihe abavuga gutyo bari 12% mu kwa gatanu, bakaba bari 7% mu kwa gatatu
 Ariko hari igice kinini c’abanyamerika bashigikiye ko iyo mfashanyo ibandanya itangwa – bangana na 73% mu ntango z’uku kwezi nk’uko biri mu biharuro bitangazwa na Reuters/Ipsos
 Mu gihe kazoza k’imfashanyo y’igihe kirekire ya Amerika kuri Ukraine kadatomoye, Herbst  abona ko abanyagihugu bazobandanya babishigikiye mu gihe abanyaporitike bobisigura neza
 Ati: "Urashobora gushira hamwe impande zompi muri Amerika, imigambwe yompi ikavuga ururimi rumwe yerekana ingaruka mbi [z’ibikorwa vy’Uburusiya muri Ukraine]"
 "Mu gihe ibi vyoba, nta nkeka ko no mu myaka ibiri canke itatu iri imbere, Abanyamerika bazoba bashigikiye ko uburyo bwozotangwa nk’uko buriko buratangwa uno musi”

Umugabo wo muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yari amaze hafi imyaka 40 ari mw’ibohero yagiriwe n’icaha c’ubwicanyi yarekuwe inyuma y’ibipimo vya ADN/DNA vyerekana ko iki caha cakozwe n’uwundi muntu
 Maurice Hastings yari amaze imyaka irenga 38 ari mw’ibohero ku bwicanyi bwo mu 1983 bwakorewe Roberta Wydermyer mu ntara ya California, hamwe n’ibindi vyaha bibiri vyo kugerageza kwica
 Ariko ivyemezo bishasha vy’ibipimo vya ADN vyerekana ahubwo ko ubu bwicanyi bwakozwe n’uwundi mugabo yapfiriye mw’ibohero mu 2020
 Umushikirizamanza w’akarere ka Los Angeles, George Gascón, avuga ko intahe yakubiswe ari “akarenganyo katagira izina”
 Mw’itangazo, avuga ati: "Inzego z’ubutungane ntizitunganye, kandi iyo tubonye ivyemezo bishasha bidutuma dutakaza icizere mu rubanza, ni ngombwa ko twihuta gufata ingingo”
 Roberta Wydermyer yatowe yapfiriye mu kibanza gishirwamwo imizigo c’inyuma mu modoka yiwe afise igikomere c’urusasu rumwe mu mutwe mu 1983
 Imbere y’aha yari yabanje gufatwa ku nguvu
 Hastings yaje kwagirizwa icaha c’ubwicanyi, abashikirizamanza bakaba barondeye kumucira igihano co kunyongwa
 Inyuma y’aho vyankiye ko umurwi wa mbere w’abacamanza wumvikana ku rubanza bomucira, uwundi wa kabiri waramukubise intahe mu gahanga hanyuma mu 1988 umucira gupfungwa ubuzima bwiwe bwose kandi ko atazigera atezurirwa
 Igihe hakorwa ivyigwa vyo kwa muganga kugira barabe icari camwishe, bamusanzemwo intanga (amasohoro mu Kinyarwanda) mu kanwa
 Hastings yabandanije asigura ko yera kuva agifatwa, ariko mu 2000 umushikirizamanza w’akarere yaranse ko hakorwa ibipimo vya ADN kuri izo ntanga
 Ariko amaherezo, mu 2021 yarashoboye kwereka umurwi ujejwe gukurikirana imanza ziba zaciye mu biro vy’umushikirizamanza ko ata caha yakoze, hanyuma ibipimo vya ADN vyakozwe mu kwa gatandatu bikaba vyerekanye ko izo ntanga zitari rwiwe
 Iyo ADN ahubwo basanze ari iy’umugabo yagiriwe n’icaha co kunyuruza umuntu akoresheje ikirwanisho, aca ashira umugore yari ahejeje kwica mu kibanza gishirwamwo imizigo c’inyuma mu modoka (boot/ coffre)
 Inyuma y’aho sentare isasiye ku wa 20 Gitugutu (10) igafuta urubanza, Hastings yabwiye abanyamakuru ko ata burakari afise, ko ico yipfuza ari ukunezerwa mu buzima asigaje
 Ikinyamakuru Associated Press  gisubiramwo Hastings  avuga ati: "Narasenze imyaka myinshi nsaba ko uyu musi woshika
 Ntawe ndiko ndatunga intoke; si ndi umuntu yarakaye, ariko nipfuza kunezererewa ubuzima ko ubu ndabufise”

Paul Pelosi, umugabo w’umukuru w’inama nshingamateka ya Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Nancy Pelosi, ariko aratora mitende aho abagiwe inyuma y’igitero n’umuntu yari yitwaje inyundo muhira iwe
 Paul Pelosi w’imyaka 82 afise igikomere mu mutwe, akaba kandi yakomerekejwe cane ku kuboko kw’i buryo n’ibiganza
 Uwakoze ico gitero avugwa ko yategetse ko bamwereka Nancy Pelosi inyuma yo kumena akinjira ku nguvu mu muhana wabo uri i San Francisco
 Perezida Joe Biden abona ko iki gitero gishingiye ku mvo za poritike kandi ko ari ico “agasuzuguro”
 Umugabo w’imyaka 42 yarahagaritswe yagirizwa ivyaha birimwo gushaka kwica
 Nta mvo gushika ubu iramenyekana
 Nancy Pelosi – yari ku mugwa mukuru w’igihugu i Washington DC igihe iki gitero caba – yaciye asubira inyuma kuraba umugabo wiwe mu bitaro
 Umuvugizi w’uyu mutegetsi wo hejuru mu mugambwe w’aba Democrats avuga ko Paul Pelosi yatewe mu masaha y’agatondo k’ejo ku wa gatanu “n’umwicanyi mubi, yamuteye ubwoba ko yari kumwica aramutse atamweretse ahari umukuru w’inama nshingamateka”
 Yaciye arazwa mu bitaro bikuru vya Zuckerberg i San Francisco kugira bamubage, abanganga bakaba biteze ko akira neza, nk’uko Drew Hammill, umuvugizi wa Nancy Pelosi, abivuga
 Mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru, umukuru w’igipolisi i San Francisco William Scott avuga ko abapolisi batewe akamo nk’isaha 11h27 mu masaha yo mu Burundi no mu Rwanda ejo ku wa gatanu baca baja gutabara
 Basanze Paul Pelosi n’uwamuteye – abapolisi bavuga ko yitwa David DePape – bariko barwanira inyundo, ariko ko uyo yamuteye yari yamunesheje arayimwaka, ari nayo yamukubitishije nabi
 Paul Pelosi yakubiswe iyo nyundo incuro n’imiburiburi imwe, nk’uko bivugwa n’igipolisi
 Abapolisi baciye bafata uyo nyene gukora ico gitero baca bamwaka ikirwanisho ciwe
 Inyamiramabi zabwiye ikinyamakuru CBS News ko yashatse kuboha Paul “gushika Nancy ashitse muhira”
 Avugwa ko mu gihe ivyo vyaba yakomye akaruru avuga ngo: “Nancy ari he?” Umukuru w’igipolisi i San Francisco Scott avuga kandi ko uwakoze ibi yagirizwa gukora igitero afise ikirwanisho cica, kumena inzu, hamwe n’ibindi vyaha bitari bike
 Scott yabwiye abanyamakuru ko uwagirizwa gukora iki gitero ari mu bitaro, ariko akaba ata nsiguro yatanze ku kungene amerewe
 Ikinyamakuru Los Angeles Times kivuga ko igihe iki gitero gitangura, Paul Pelosi yabwiye uyu yari yamuteye ko yashaka kuja kwoga, hanyuma aca ahamagara igipolisi mw’ibanga kuri terefone yiwe ngendanwa kandi aca ayisiga yuguruye, bituma uwamwakiriye kuri terefone yumva ingene yariko avugana n’uwari yamuteye
 Mu gihe yariko ashikiriza ijambo mu myiyamamazo i Philadelphia, Perezida Biden yavuze ko ubukozi bw’ikibi bushingiye kuri poritike ata “kibanza bugifise” muri Amerika, kandi ko “bukwiye guhagarara”
 Ati: "Buri muntu yiyumvira neza ategerezwa guhaguruka akiyamiriza atarya umunwa ubukozi bw’ikibi muri poritike yacu”
 Umukuru w’abakenguzamateka bo mu mugambwe w’aba Repubulika Mitch McConnell avuga ko yababajwe cane n’iki gitero
 Nancy Pelosi ni umwe mu banya poritike bakomeye cane mu gihugu
 Yatorewe ikiringo kigira kane nk’umukuru w’inama nshingamateka mu 2021, akaba aza ubwa kabiri inyuma y’icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu Kamala Harris
 Ubu ari mu myiyamamazo yongera yegeranya uburyo mu gihugu kw’izina ry’aba Democrats imbere y’amatora y’abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka yimirije ku wa 08 Munyonyo uno mwaka
 Amasaha make imbere y’iki gitero, reta yari yasohoye ubutumwa bwahawe inyamiramabi mu gihugu cose bugabisha ko hashobora kuba ibitero ku mihana y’abahiganwa n’abajejwe gutegura amatora bishobora gukorwa n’abantu bafise ivyo batishimiye muri poritike
 Umugabo wiwe, umutunzi ruhebwa, asanzwe aba i San Francisco, ari naho yavukiye akanakurira
 Bubakanye kuva mu 1963 bakaba bafitaniye abana batanu
 Abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka bama bagavye cane ku mutekano wabo kuva habaye ca gitero ku ngoro y’amakoraniro y’inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka (Capitol) mu kwa mbere 2021
