Abagize Inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano kw’isi basubiriye gushikiriza impungenge bafise kw’ivyuka ry’umuhari w’inyeshamba wa M23 n’iyindi mirwi y’inyeshamba irangwa mu buseruko bwa Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo
 Mw’itangazo iyo Nama yaraye isohoye, yasubiye kwiyamiriza yivuye inyuma imirwi y’inyeshamba ikiyogoza muri ico gihugu, yaba iyo hagati mu gihugu canke iyiva hanze
 Amakuru ava mu karere k’Ubuseruko bwa Congo avuga ko intambara zibica bigacika hagati y’ingabo za Congo (FARDC) n’umuhari M23 mu micungararo ya Rutshuru no mu bindi bisagara
 Abagize iyo Nama basaba imirwi yose  yitwaje ibirwanisho guhagarika ubugizi bwa nabi idatevye hanyuma imihari y’inyeshamba  ya Congo nayo ikitabira, ataco irinze gusaba, umugambi wo gusubiza ibirwanisho no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe
 Isaba kandi imirwi y’inyeshamba iva hanze gushira ibirwanisho hasi idatevye hanyuma igasubira mu bihugu yaje ivamwo
