 Muri uku  guhiganirwa uburongozi, Sunak yaronse abashingamateka bamushigikira hakiri  kare, kandi adatevye
 Yarengeje amazina y’abashingamateka bakenewe 100 imbere y’uko ikiringo ntarengwa gihera - harimwo n’ay'abashingamateka bahoze bashigikiye Liz Truss canke Boris Johnson
 Mu guhiganira uburongozi mu gihe caheruka, ntiyahuje na gato n’uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere, yavuga ko integuro yiwe yo kugurana amafaranga mu gihe ifaranga ririko ritakaza agaciro bisa n’urwenya rushoborora guta ubutunzi mu kaga
 Abavyeyi biwe baje mu Bwongereza bavuye muri Africa y’Ubuseruko kandi amamuko yabo bose ni Ubuhindi
 Sunak yavukiye muri Southampton mu 1980, aho se wiwe yari asanzwe ari umuganga, nyina wiwe nawe atwara iduka ry'imiti
 Ni we wa mbere abaye umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubwongereza ava muri Asia
 Sunak yabaye umushingamateka mu 2015- wo muri Richmond muri Yorkshire-ariko yaciye aduga cane mu gihe gito aba umushikiranganji ajejwe ubutunzi – mu kwezi kwa kabiri mu 2020 mu gihe Boris Johnson yari umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Nk’uwujejwe ubutunzi igihe ca Johnson, Sunak niwe yatanguje umugambi w'imfashanyo y’amafaranga mu gihe ca guma mu rugo – harimwo amafaranga yagenewe abakuwe ku kazi be n’umugambi bise ‘’Eat out to help out’’ wari ujejwe gufasha ibibanza vy’uburiro kugira bigume bikora
 Umugore wiwe Akshata Murthy, ni umukobwa w’umutunzi ruhebwa mu Buhindi, Narayana Murthy
