 Ikinyamakuru The Sunday Times Rich List kigereranya ko uwyo muryango ufise umutungo w’amafranga ungana hafi imiriyoni 730 z'amapawundi (£:amafranga y’Ubwongereza)
 Mu ci, vyagaragaye ko Akshata Murthy atarishe amakori y'Ubwongereza ku nyungu nini yakura hanze - kandi biri mu mategeko
 Sunak yarashigikiye umugore wiwe avuga ati "gucafuza umugore wanje undondera ni bibi cane" – ariko yahavuye yemera gutangura kuriha ayo makori yiyongera ku yo yatanga
