Hari ikintu kidasanze mu mateka y’Ubushinwa caraye kibaye ejo ku wa Mungu: ikoraniro kaminuza ry’Umugambwe w‘Abakomunista (Congress of the Communist Party (CCP)  rigira 20, iri rikaba risanzwe riba uko imyaka itanu irangiye mu ntumbero yo kwemeza uwurongora iki gihugu rutura co ku mugabane wa Aziya, ryaraye rihaye umukuru w’igihugu ahari ubu, Xi Jinping, ikiringo kigira gatatu yikurikiranya, ibitari bwigere bibaho
 Iyi ngingo, yiyongereye kw’ihindurwa ry’ibwirizwashingiro  mu 2018 ryakuyeho ingingo yategeka ko ata mukuru w’igihugu ashobora kurenza ibiringo bibiri, igiye kwongerereza inguvu Xi mu kugenzura Ubushinwa, mu kumugira, nk’uko abenshi mu bihweza ibintu n’ibindi babivuga, umukuru w’igihugu wa mbere akomeye kuva ku washinze Repubulika y’Ubushinwa, Mao Zedong
 Kimwe mu vyo Xi yemereye abanyagihugu igihe atorwa mu buryo butari bwitezwe kuba umunyamabanga mukuru ni uko CCP itazobona amahano nk’ayo Umugambwe w’Abakomunista w’Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti (URSS/USSR) wasenyutse mu 1991
 Isenyuka rya URSS – gushika ico gihe yafatirwako akarorero n’Ubushinwa – ryateje ibibazo abategetsi benshi b’Ubushinwa, ariko nta bavyitayeho nk’uko Xi avyitayeho
 Joseph Torigian, umwigisha kw’ishure kaminuza  School of International Service of China, yabwiye BBC Mundo ati: “Xi Jinping yavutse mu 1953 kandi ico gihe inyigisho ngenderwako yakoreshwa cane mu Bushinwa yari: 'Reta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abasoviyeti uyu munsi ni Ubushinwa bw'ejo'
” Uyu mwigisha wa kaminuza akongera akaba n’umuhinga muri poritike z’Uburusiya n’iz’Ubushinwa avuga kandi ati:  “Rimwe mu majambo ya mbere kandi akomeye ya Xi yashikirije igihe ashika ku butegetsi ryari ryerekeye isenyuka ry’Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti”
 Xi yaryise ko ari “imburi”
 Muri ino nkuru tugiye kurabira hamwe ibintu bitatu nyamukuru Xi yigiye kw’isenyuka ry’Abasoviyeti n’ingene vyamufashije kuguma arongoye CCP igihe kirekire kuva kuri Mao
 Mw’ijambo Xi yashikirije abarongoye  CCP  – ijambo ryabacorotse kandi ryakunzwe gusubirwamwo – yavuze ko isenyuka rya URSS ryatumwe n’itituka ry’indero (discipline) mu mugambwe, n’uko ata muntu yari ajejwe akarangamutima k’umugambwe
 “Kubera iki Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti bwasenyutse? Kubera iki Umugambwe w’Abakomunista w’Abasoviyeti wasenyutse?” bivugwa ko ari vyo yama abaza bagenziwe
 “Imvo nyamukuru ni uko ivyiyumviro n’akarangamutima kayo vyatitutse”
 Hagati aho, nk’uko abivuga, igihe uwari arongoye igihugu ico gihe, Mikhail Gorbachev,  afatiye ingingo yo kuzana impinduka zavuyemwo isenyuka ry’ubutegetsi bw’Abasoviyeti, nta n’umwe yamwiyamirije
 Xi yasubiwemwo avuga ati: "Amaherezo ya vyose, ryabaye ijambo rituje rya Gorbachev avuga ko Umugambwe w’Abakomunista b’Abasoviyeti usambutse, umugambwe rutura urazimangana”
 Mu majambo yo kunegura, avuga ati: "Impera ya vyose, harabuze umugabo nya mugabo
 Nta n’umwe yubahutse guhagarara bwuma”
 Ku wa 01 Mukakaro (7)  2021, mw’ijambo yashikirije mu birori vyo guhimbaza imyaka 100 y’umugambwe CCP, Xi – yari asanzwe atavugira ku mugaragaro kenshi mu myaka cumi amaze ku butegetsi – yashimangiye akamaro k’umugambwe
 Ati: “Umugambwe ni rwo ruti rw’umugono rw’Ubushinwa
 Iterambere ry’Ubushinwa rishingiye ku mugambwe”
 Umunyamakuru w’Ubuyapani Katsuji Nakazawa yandika mu kinyamakuru gikomeye co muri Aziya Nikkei Aziya, yavuze ko “gushiraho ubutegetsi bw’umugambwe umwe - uburyo bwiwe bwo gukingira Ubushinwa ivyashikiye Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti – niyo poritike yonyene Xi agenderako kandi yahagarariye ku butegesi bwiwe”
 Imwe mu ngingo za mbere Xi yafashe ashikiriye ubutegetsi yabaye gushinga “imirwi mito mito” itari mike muri komite nkuru y’umugambwe, ari nayo yavuyemwo inzego nkuru  zifata imigambi mikuru y'igihugu
 Xi we nyene ubwiwe ni we yarongoye iyi mirwi
  Yafashe ubutegetsi bwose mu minwe hanyuma agabanya ubushobozi bw’Inama nkuru y’igihugu (State Council/ Conseil des affaires de l'État), inama nshikiranganji irongowe na Li Keqiang, umukeba wa Xi muri poritike
 Inkurikizi y’ibi, na poritike y’ubutunzi yari isanzwe irongowe n’umushikiranganji wa mbere buhoro buhoro yahavuye ayigarurira
 Ikindi mu mayeri yakoresheje kuva mu ntango mu ntumbero yo gutsimbataza umugambwe kugira ngo ntusambuke, kwabaye ugutanguza amasekeza akomeye yo gutuza ibiturire
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe ryo kwugurura ikoraniro rigira 20 rya CCP ku wa Mungu uheze, yemereye abari aho ko reta yiwe “yakuyeho inzitizi zikomeye zari zinyegeje mu mugambwe”, kubera poritike yiwe
 Hagati aho, abenshi mu bihweza ibintu n’ibindi babona ko aya masekeza yabaye ugukura imitego yari kumuzibira mu gutsimbataza ubutegetsi bwiwe, akuraho abashobora kumubera abakeba
 Ibihumbi amajana n’amajana y’abategetsi b’umugambwe w’Abakomunista baragirijwe kurya ibiturire, ibi bica bituma Xi atanguza impinduka mu mugambwe, aho nyene ariko aba kibirengeye muri CCP
 Carl Minzner, umwanditsi w’igitabo “End of an Era: How China’s Authoritarian Revival Is Undermining Its Rise,” aherutse kubwira ikinyamakuru New York Times, ati: “Inguvu zose Xi – mu kugenzura gusumba amarangamutima, kwemeza ko umugambwe wiganje mu gihugu cose, be no gusubiza Pekin/Beijing mu butegetsi bw’umuntu umwe – zifise intumbero yo gukingira Ubushinwa kugira ngo ntibuhave bugwa mu mutego nk’uwo [Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti] bwaguyemwo”
 Minzner, umunywanyi w’ikigo c’abahinga ca Amerika,  American Council on Foreign Relations, abona ko iki ari igihushane, kuko, mu gihe anegura Abakomunista b’Abasoviyeti baretse Gorbachev agafata ingingo wenyene kw’isenyuka rya URSS, ukwigungirako ubutegetsi bwose n’ukwigira ikimana, ibi bikibutsa ubutegetsi bwa Mao, biriko bijana hamwe
 Ati: “Igitangaje ni uko inzira Xi yahisemwo ishobora gusubiza Ubushinwa mu buryo ntasubira inyuma mu bihe vya kera vy’ubutegetsi canke ikabushira mu bihe Uburusiya burimwo iki gihe, aho intwaro yose igendera kw’ishaka ry’umuntu umwe rudende”
 Ikindi cigwa gikomeye umukuru w’igihugu c’Ubushinwa yakuye mw’isenyuka ry’Umugambwe w’Abakomunista b’Abasoviyeti ni akamaro ko kugira igisirikare gikomeye kandi kikuyoboka
 Torigian  ati: “Xi abona ko ari ikintu ngirakamaro ko umugambwe ugenzura igisirikare, kugira ngo iyo hadutse akaguma, nka kamwe ko mu 1989 ku kibanza ca Tiananmen Square, gishobore kukazimya gikoresheje inguvu”
 Nk’uko uyu muhinga abivuga, kurya abona ko gukomeza umugambwe ari ukuwufata mu minwe, niko yakoze no mu gisirikare rutura, kizwi nka People’s Liberation Army (PLA) c’Ubushinwa
 Ati: “N’aho ata bubasha kama afise kuri PLA, nk’uko vyari bimeze kuri Mao Zedong na Deng Xiaoping, bazwi ko bari abategetsi bakomeye mu gihe c’impinduka (revolution), mu kiringo c’imyaka itari mike,  Xi Jinping yaritayeho kugiriranira ubucuti n’igisirikare , aduza abantu bari bamwegereye, hamwe rero n’abajejwe akarangamutima bama bibutsa igisirikare ko ari we mutegetsi mukuru”
 Nk’uko Torigian abivuga,  “Xi yifata ko ari we buraro n’uburamuko mu bijanye n’umutekano w’igihugu kandi ko akeneye kugenzura igisirikare mu gihe hokwaduka ikintu kigeramiye ubutegetsi, caba ikiva hagati canke hanze y’igihugu”
 Mu vy’ukuri, ni we agenzura “inyabutatu ya gikomunista”  - Umugambwe, Reta, n’Ingabo -  ari co gituma abenshi mu bihweza ibintu n’ibindi bafata Xi nk’umukuru w’igihugu wa mbere akomeye kuva kuri Mao
 Xi ntiyifatiye mu minwe PLA  gusa, yarayikomeje, mu kwongereza amafaranga ikoresha, mu gushinga uturere twa gisirikare, mu kwongereza imyimenyerezo ya gisirikare mu ntumbero yo kwitegurira intambara yokwaduka, hamwe no kwagura ububiko bw’ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri, ikintu giteye impungenge Uburengero, nk’uko Torigian  abivuga
 Ibi vyose birajanye n’ikindi kimwe kiri mu ngingo ngenderwako yigiye kw’isenyuka ry’Abasoviyeti: “Igihugu gikomeye gitegerezwa kugira igisirikare gikomeye, kuko ni ubu buryo bwonyene gishobora gukingira ubutaka bwaco”, nk’uko yabivuze mw’ijambo ryiwe mu birori vyo guhimbaza imyaka 100 y’umugambwe CCP
 Ku wa Mungu uheze, yarashimangiye ubu butumwa, mu kuvuga ko intumbero y’umugambwe ari “ukwubaka igisirikare gikomeye muri kino gihe gishasha”
 Nk’uko abahinga babivuga, Xi yagarutse kw’ijambo “umutekano” incuro zirenga 70 mw’ijambo ryiwe, harimwo kandi no kugabisha Taiwan, igihugu Ubushinwa bufata ko ari ubutaka bwabwo
 Xi kandi yarigiye mu ngorane z’Abasoviyeti ko ategerezwa kugenzura poritike n’akarangamutima vy’umugambwe n’igisirikare
 Abonye ingene igihugu cari kinini gusumba ibindi vyose kw’isi ico gihe gisambaguritse, inyuma y’isenyuka ry’umugambwe w’Abakomunista, kigacikamwo ibihugu vyinshi bishasha, yarabonye ko kugira ngo Ubushinwa bugume mu bumwe, yategerezwa gutuza abantu bose batavuga rumwe, baba abo hagati mu gihugu canke hanze
 Nico gituma adahesha, atari kuri  Taiwan giusa - "Gusubiza hamwe igihugu cacu ni ngombwa kandi bitegerezwa gukorwa”, nk’uko yagabishije ku wa Mungu – canke kuri Hong Kong, ubutaka bwasubijwe Ubushiwa mu 1997 ariko Pekin igashinga itegeko rijanye n’umutekano w’igihugu mu ntumbero yo gutuza imyiyerekano y’abarondera intwaro rusangi
 Ubushinwa kandi burarwanya abanyagihugu bo mu bwoko bw’aba Uyghur  hagati mu gihugu, mu kwugaranira ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’aba banyagihugu b’aba-Islam mu bibanza bapfungiwemwo mu ntara ya Xinjiang, itoteza, nk’uko icegeranyo c’ishirahamwe ONU kibivuga, “rishobora kuba ivyaha mpuzamakungu, cane cane ivyaha bikorewe kiremwa muntu”
 Yarakomeje kandi igenzura ry’igisata c’abikorera utwabo mu myaka iheze, aho yibanze cane cane ku buhinga n’igisata c’indero kiri mu minwe y’abigenga
 Nk’uko abamunegura babivuga, ikiza ca coronavirus hamwe na poritike ya “covid-zero” vyahaye icitwazo Xi na CCP co kwugarana Ubushinwa kw’isi, atari mu ntumbero yo kuzibira umugera gusa, ariko kandi n’abanyamahanga bashobora guhungabanya ubutumwa bwa gikomunista
 Hagati aho, gushinga ikizwi nka " Great Chinese Firewall " – ubuhinga bw’ico gihugu bwo kugenzura ikirere nyabwonko (cyberspace) no kuzibira imbuga ngurukanabumenyi z’Uburengero, harimwo, Facebook, Google, Twitter na Wikipedia – bwatumye uyu mukuru w’igihugu c’Ubushinwa agenzura ihanahana ry’amakuru, kuva ku makuru acishwa mu binyamakuru vyari bimenyerewe gushika no ku makuru acishwa ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi
 Ibi bizorondera kuzibira glasnost ntihave ishika mu Bushinwa, iyi ikaba ari potirike ya Gorbachev yo kwugurura imiryango yatumye igenzura ry’amakuru ryakorwa n’Abasivoyeti rihagarara, maze abanyagihugu benshi batangura kubaza ibibazo abategetsi

Rishi Sunak  agiye kuba umushikiranganji wa mbere  wa UK wa mbere w’amamuko ya Asia
 Ni inyuma y’aho uwo bari kumwe mw’ihiganwa asokoreye mu kurondera kuba umukuru w’umugambwe w’aba Conservative (canke Tory)
 Hafi abashingamateka 200 b’aba Conservative bashigikiye ku mugaragaro uwo yahoze ari umushikirikiranganji ajejwe ikigega mu gihe igenwa ryategerezwa kurangira uyu munsi
 Umukuru w’inama nshingamateka Penny Mordaunt yasokoye aho ananirirwe no kuronka abamushigikira bakwiye mu bashingakateka imbere y’uko igihe ntarengwa kirangira isaha umunani z’umuhingamo mu masaha yo mu Bwongereza
 Bisigura ko Sunak agiye gusubirira Liz Truss  mu kibanza c’umushikiranganji wa mbere inyuma y’aho ibivuye mw’ihiganwa bitangarijwe na Sir Graham Brady, umukuru w’umugwi 1922 utunganya itorwa ry’umukuru w’aba Tory
  Umwami Charles III azoca agena Sunak kugira asubirire Liz Truss yatanze imihoho ku ndwi iheze amaze iminsi 45 gusa ku butegetsi
 Gutorwa kwa Sunak kuba umukuru w’aba Tory kubaye ukugaruka vuba cane kw’uwo yahora ari umushikiranganji ajejwe ikigega  inyuma yo kurushwa mw’ihiganwa n’uwo asubiriye  mu minsi iheze
 Imigambwe itavuga rumwe n’uwuri ku butegetsi yo imaze iminsi isaba ko haba amatora rusangi ivuga ko Sunak adafise inshingano ya democrasi co kuba umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Ayandi matora rusangi ntiyitezwe imbere nibura mu 2024 uhereye aho aba Conservative batsindiye ayaheruka  ku majwi menshi cane mu 2019
 S﻿unak yavukiye i Southampton mu 1980 ku bavyeyi bamuka muri Punjab mu Buhindi bimukiye mu Bwongereza mu myaka ya 1960 bavuye muri Afrika y'Ubuseruko

Ukraine iriyamiriza ibivugwa n’Uburusiya ko Kyiv (umugwa mukuru wa Ukraine) ishobora gukoresha “ibombe y’umwanda”  - ibibombe bisanzwe bivangwa n’ubumara (matières radioactives)
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky avuga ko ibi vyerekana ko Uburusiya bwonyene bushobora kuba buriko butegura gukora igitero nk’iki
 Incuti za Ukraine nazo nyene ziriyamiriza ibi bivugwa n’Uburusiya, mbere Amerika ikiyamiriza “icitwazo ico ari co cose cotuma ibintu biyangara”
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi w’Uburusiya Sergei Shoigu yavuze ivy’amabombe y’umwanda mu gihe yavugana na mugenziwe w’Ubwongereza Ben Wallace kuri terefone
 Yavuze ko afise “amakenga ku gishobora kuba agasotoro ka Kyiv karimwo ikoreshwa ry’ibombe y’umwanda”
 Ku wa Mungu, Shoigu yagiranye kandi ibiganiro n’abashikiranganji bo kwivuna abansi ba Amerika, Ubufaransa na Turukiya, abashikiriza impungenge za Moscou
 Nta vyemezo yatanze bishigikira ivyo yagiriza Ukraine
 Mu kwishura kuri ibi, Perezida Zelensky yagiriza Uburusiya ko ari bwo “ntandaro y’ibintu vyose vy’umwanda bishobora kuba muri ino ntambara”
 Avuga ko Uburusiya buriko butera ubwoba isi bukoresheje “akaga k’inguvu z’ubumara” ku kigo ca nikleyeri ca Zaporizhzhia bwigaruriye
 Anavuga kw’iterabwoba rya Moscou ryo kumena urugomero rukomeye rwo mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya) iriyamiriza ibi birego
 Umukuru wa Ukraine kandi arashimangira ko “amakungu yofata ingingo zose zikomeye zishoboka”
 Hagati aho, Wallace avuga ko yamiriye kure ibivugwa na Shoigu ko "Ukraine iriko itegura imigambi ifashwe mu mugongo n’ibihugu vy’Uburengero, harimwo n’Ubwongereza, yo gutuma ibintu biyangara muri Ukraine”
 Yagabishije kandi ko ibirego nk’ibi "bitoba icitwazo co gukora ikintu cotuma ibintu vyunyuka”
 Amajambo nk’ayo kandi niyo yavuzwe n’umunyamabanga wa Amerika ajejwe kwivuna abansi, Lloyd Austin, igihe yavugana na Shoigu ejo ku wa Mungu, mu kiganiro kigira kabiri nawe kuri terefone mu misi mike cane
 Mw’itangazo rusangi, abashikiranganji bajejwe imigenderanire b’ibihugu vy’Ubufaransa, Ubwongereza na Amerika bavuze ko ibihugu vyabo “vyiyamirije amajambo y’ikinyoma ceruye ko Ukraine iriko itegura gukoresha ibombe y’umwanda ku butaka bwayo”, banavuga ko bazobandanya bafata mu mugongo Ukraine "muri ino ntambara y’ubugome ya Perezida Putin"
 Abihweza ibintu n’ibindi mu gisirikare bavuga ko ivyo Uburusiya bwagiriza Ukraine bije inyuma y’aho bugize imisi butsindwa ahatari hake, be no mu gihe ingabo za Ukraine zibandanya ibitero vyo kwivuna mu buseruko no mu bumanuko bw’igihugu
 Mu rukurikirane rw’ubutumwa cacishije ku rubuga rwa Twitter, ikigo ca Amerika cigisha ivy’intambara, Institute for the Study of War (ISW), kivuga ko Shoigu "asa n’uwariko arondera guhagarika canke kugabanya umurindi w’imfashanyo za gisirikare Uburengero buha Ukraine, hamwe kandi kumbure no kurondera ingene aca intege urunani rwa OTAN/NATO  mu kurutera ubwoba”
 Hagati aho, ISW yongerako iti: "Kremlin ntavyo irimwo vyo gutegura igitero ca vuba ca bombe y’umwanda
 Ibivugwa na Shoigu bije gukomeza isekeza ry’akarimi Uburusiya bumazemwo igihe kirekire”
