 M﻿u gihe abashingamateka bose boja inyuma y'umukandida umwe, hashobora kuboneka umushikiranganji wa mbere mushasha ku wa mbere inyuma y'umutaga
 A﻿riko bitabaye ivyo, hazoba amatora ku mbuga hwaniro y'abayoboke bose b'umugambwe w'aba conservateurs, ivyayavuyemwo bikazomenyekana ku musi wa gatanu
 I﻿biharuro vyo kugereranya vyerekana ko Johnson, yagarutse avuye mu karuhuko mu mazinga ya Caraïbes kugira yihweze ico yokora, yoba aza imbere mu kwegeranya amajwi menshi y'abanywanyi
 K﻿u musi wa gatandatu wose, abashingamateka bawumaze bamenyesha ku mugaragaro uwo bashigikiye muri ayo matora
 S﻿unak yashigikiwe n'abashingamateka bavuye mu bice vyose vy'umugambwe wiwe, harimwo n'abantu bamenyekana cane nk'uwahoze ari umuyobozi mwishikira wa Johnson, Steve Barclay, uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wiwe wa Brexit, Lord Frost, Kemi Badenoch umunyamabanga nwa reta ajejwe ubudandaji mpuzamakungu hamwe n'umushikiranganji wa Irlande yo mu buraruko, Steve Baker
