  Aya n’amatohoza y’ivyaha ashobora kuvamwo kwagirizwa ivyaha
 Kimwe mu vyo ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane buvuga n’uko Trump ashobora kuba yararenze ku ngingo yitwa “Espionage Act”  mu kubika inyandiko zerekeye umutekano w’igihugu “zishobora gukoreshwa mu kugirira nabi Reta Zunze Ubumwe
” Uretse ivyaha bijanye n’izo nyandiko zo mw’ibanga ubwazo, abashikirizamanza bariko barakora kandi amatohoza y’ukubera intambanyi ubutungane nk’ikindi gishobora kuba icaha
 Abunganira Trump baracari mu mpari zijanye n’amateko n’ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane  kuri ayo matohoza
 Abashikirizamanza i New York bariko barakora amatohoza kuri Trump Organisation, yahoze ari kompanyi y’umuryango y’uwo yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu
 I New York hariko haraba amatohoza abiri: -rimwe risanzwe n’irindi ry’ivyaha
 Letitia James, umushikirizamanza mukuru wa New York, arongoye iryo tohoza risanzwe (iryo ntirijana kwagirizwa ivyaha) akaba amaze hafi imyaka itatu ariko aratohoza niba iyo kompanyi yarakoze amanyanga atandukanye ku myaka mirongo muri iyo ntara
 Muri ivyo harimwo guha agaciro karenze urugero amatungo  nk’ibibuga vya golf canke amahoteri, kugira aronke amadeni y’inyungu nto n’urugero rwiza rwo guharurirwako amakori
 Itohoza rijanye n’ivyaha, ku rundi ruhande, rirongowe n’umushikirizamanza mukuru ya District ya Manhattan Alvin  Bragg, kandi nawe nyene akaba ariko akora ku kibazo kimwe, kuko iryo tohoza ryerekeye ibikorwa vy’i New York
 Uwo yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu n’abamwunganira bavuga ko kompanyi ata na kimwe yakoze kinyuranye n’amategeko
 Yagirije Madame James, umu-democrat, kurondera kwihora muri poritike, aho akagaruka ku majambo yavuze imbere y’uko atorwa kuba umushkirizamanza mukuru aho yarahiye ko azomwitwarira akamwita “umukuru w’igihugu atemewe”
 Igihe yahamagarwa kuja kubazwa mu matohoza asanzwe, Trump yaranse kwishura ibibazo yemeza gusa izina ryiwe
 Madame James  yarashingishije urubanza rw’amanyanga [yoba yakozwe na kompanyi ya Trump] mu kwezi kwa Nyakanga, urubanza  rushobora  gutuma iyo kompanyi  idasubira kubaho uko iri gushika ubu
 Madame James yavuze ko uwo yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu, abana batatu ba mbere biwe hamwe na babiri mu bategetsi ba kompanyi, bakoze ibikorwa bitandukanye vy’amanyanga  hagati ya 2011 na 2021
 Muri urwo rubanza rwashingishijwe, umuryango wagirizwa kwerekana inyungu irengeye cane  iy’ukuri, rukaba rurondera miriyoni 250 z’ama dorari waronse biciye mu buryo bw’amanyanga
 Rurondera kandi ko Trump n’abana biwe bafatirwa ingingo z’ibihano vyo kutemererwa kuja mu kibanza c’uburungozi mu gikorwa c’ubugwizatunga ico arico cose i New York
 Itohoza ry’ivyaha gushika ubu  ntaco kivugwako cane
 Madame James, ariko, ivyo yatoye yarabirungikiye abashikirizamanza b’igihugu kandi bishobora gufasha mw’itohoza rishasha rigiye kwugururwa
 Ibivugwa nk’uruhara Trump ashobora kuba yaragize mu gitero ca US Capitol  itariki 6 Nzero mu 2021, igihe isinzi ry’abantu bamushigikiye batera iyo nyubakwa barondera kubuza ko intsinzi mu matora ya prezida Joe Biden yemezwa, biriko biratohozwa n’inzego zitandukanye z’igihugu
 Uwugaragara cane n’umugwi w’inama nkenguzamateka na nshingamateka ugize igihe uriko uratohoza ku bikorwa vya Trump
 Barumvirije abantu vyerekanwa ku mboneshakure,barondera kwerekana ko ivyo Trump yavuze ko amatora yibwe vyatumye  haba imigumuko mu buryo butaziguye
 Hari kandi n’amatohoza y’ivyaha y’ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane ku vyabaye ku wa 6 Nzero no kurondera mu buryo bwagutse kuburizamwo ivyavuye mu matora – ariko ivyo ahanini vyagumijwe mw’ibanga
 Niyo matohoza ya mbere y’igiporisi akomeye cane muri kahise ka Amerika, ariko ahagarukira kuba ari Trump aronderwa ntihazwi
 Yarahakanye uruhara mu migumuko  hanyuma anegura uwo mugwi w’inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka awita “sentare ya kangaroo [sentare ya ngondagonde]”
 Yabandanije kuvuga ata vyemeza ko habaye ubusuma mu matora
 Umugwi w’inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka -ugizwe n’aba-democrat indwi n’aba-republican babiri- nta bubasha ufise bwo kuburanisha ariko bemeje batoye kurengutsa Trump
 Ivyo bisigura ko mu mategeko ategerezwa kuza kubazwa no kwishura ibibazo imbere y’inama nshingamamateka na nkenguzamateka, ariko vyitezwe ko atazokwitaba, ivyo bikazoca bivamwo urugamba rw’amategeko
 Uwo mugwi uriko uraraba kandi niba wosaba ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane ngo bwagirize Trump icaha
 Mu ngiro ibi ntaco bivuze cane, ariko bishbora kwongereza igitutu ku bakora amatohoza
 Itohoza ry’ivyaha ry’ubushikiranganji bw’ubutungane bimaze gutuma abantu amajana bateye Capitol bagirizwa ivyaha
 Uwo yahoze ari umukuru w’igihugtu ntarahamagarwa kugira abazwe muri iryo tohoza, ariko n’ikintu gishoboka
 Kandi ashobora no kwagirizwa mu gihe abakora amatohoza bobona ko hari ivyemezo bikwiye ko hari ivyaha yakoze
 Abashikirizamanza muri iyo ntara bariko baratohoza ku bivugwa ko hageragejwe kugira impfagusa ivyavuye mu matora yo mu 2020
 Iryo tohoza ry’ivyaha ryuguruwe inyuma y’aho hahishuriwe ikiyago co kuri terefone camaze isaha hagati y’uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu n’uwari ajejwe amatora ku rwego rw’igihugu itariki 2 ukwezi kwa mbere mu 2021
 Trump yabwiye umu-republican Brad Raffensperger  ico gihe ati: “Nshaka kuronka amajwi 11
780”, ayo akaba yari amajwi yari akeneye kugira atsinde muri iyo ntara ihindagura mu gutora (swing state)
 Yavuze ko iryo tohoza- co kimwe n’ayandi menshi-ari “uruhigi” [rwo kumutoteza]
 Trump yanifatiye mu gahanga uwurongoye iryo tohoza – umushikirizamanza mukuru wa Fulton County, Fani Willis - nk’umuntu akiri “muto, akirondera gushika kure, umu-democrat w’uruhande rukaze 


atwara rumwe mu nzego zamunzwe n’ivyaha hamwe n’ibiturire”
  Madame Willis yabwiye ikinyamakuru Washington Post mu kwezi guheze ati: “Ni ibintu biremereye cane
 Uwuhamijwe ivyaha hanyuma agacirirwa igihano, ashobora gucirirwa umunyororo
” Yongeyeko ati kwagirizwa muri sentare ntivyimirije kuba, ariko avuga ko Trump ashobora guhamagarwa vuba kubazwa ibibazo
 Ntibizwi niba uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu ariko arakorwako amatohoza ubwiwe mu buryo butaziguye, ariko bamwe mu bo bacuditse birazwi ko bari mu bariko barakorwa amatohoza
 Umwe muri abo ni uwahoze ari umwunganizi wiwe bwite  Rudy Giuliani, ari nawe yari  imbere mu gukoresha amategeko mu kwanka ivyavuye mu matora
 Abunganira Giuliani  bavuga ko ata caha yakoze muri iyo ntara
 Bivugwa ko abakora itohoza bariko barihweza igishobora kuba icaha mu vyo yabwiye  kuri terefone abategetsi bo muri Georgia, harimwo n’ibivugwa ko ari amatangazo y’ibinyoma yabwiye abanyaporitike aho nyene
 Ariko kugira umuntu yagirwe n’icaha, abashikirizamanza bategerezwa kwerekana, ku buryo atawobigirako amadidane, ko abatohozwako bari bazi ko ivyo bariko barakora yari amanyanga

I﻿bitero vyo mu kirere vyononye cane ibigo bitanga umuyagankuba hagati no mu burengero bwa Ukraine, mu gihe Uburusiya bubandanya gusambura intsinga z'umuyagankuba z'ico gihugu
 I﻿bibanza vyo mu bumanuko no mu burengero vyatewe, umuyagankuba uracika hirya no hino mu gihugu
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine bavuga ko milile nyinshi z'Uburusiya zakorowe n'ibisase bicungera ikirere vya Ukraine
 I﻿bice vyoba bishika kimwe ca gatatu vy'ibigo bitanga umuyagankuba  vyarasambuwe mu bitero vyo mu kirere kuva ku musi wa mbere w'indwi iheze
 K﻿u musi wa gatandatu, abategetsi ba Ukraine bavuze ko " ibikorwa remezo" vyatewe mu karere ka Cherkasy, mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bw'igisagara ca Kyiv
 Havuzwe n'urubeya rw'umuriro mwinshi hagufi y'igisagara ca Smila
 U﻿muyagankuba waracitse mu micungararo ya Khmelnytskyi, kure mu burengero
 Ibitero vyo mu kirere n'icika ry'umuyagankuba vyaravuzwe kandi muri Odesa mu bumanuko bwa Rivne na Lutsk mu buraruko bushira uburengero
 I﻿gisata gitanga umuyagankuba muri Ukraine kivuga ko gishobora kugabanya umuyagankuba gitanga mu turere twinshi harimwo na Kyiv
 R﻿eta yarashizeho itegeko rigabanya umuyagankuba ukoreshwa ubwa mbere kuva ku musi wa kane
 K﻿omanda arongoye ingabo zigwanira mu kirere muri Ukraine yavuze ko ibikoresho vyo kwikingira ibitero vyo mu kirere vyasambuye misile 18 z'Uburusiya ku wa gatandatu mu gitondo
 U﻿mukuru w'abakozi bo mu biro vya prezida Volodymyr Zelensky, Andriy Yermak, yavuze ko Uburusiya bwizeye kubuza Ukraine kubanya kwisubiza uturere mu kugira ibitero vyo mu kirere inyuma y'ahariko harabera intambara
 A﻿riko, yongeyeko ko, ivyo bitero bishobora gutuma bagira inguvu gusumba

N﻿a George Wright George Wright Iran yarungitse abahinga ba gisirikare mu karere ka Crimée/Crimea kari mu minwe y’Uburusiya mu ntumbero yo gufasha kurungika za ndege zitagira abadereva, drones, mu bitero kuri Ukraine, nk’uko bivugwa na Maison Blanche/White House
 Umuvugizi wa Amerika avuga ko aba ari abigisha n’abafasha mu vyo ubuhinga
 Ku wa mbere, umugwa mukuru wa Ukraine, Kyiv, waratewe na drones “z’ubwiyahuzi” zarungitswe n’Uburusiya ariko zizwi ko zikorwa na Irani
 Ubwongereza bwatangaje ibihano ku makompanyi n’abantu bafise uruhara mu gutanga izi drones
 Umuvugizi w’igisata kijejwe umutekano w’igihugu muri Maison Blanche, John Kirby, yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Turabona ko abasirikare ba Irani bari ku rubuga muri Crimée kandi ko bafasha Uburusiya muri ivyo bikorwa"
 Avuga ko “igitigiri gito”c’abanya-Irani bafasha mu vyo ubuhinga, Abarusiya nabo bagatwara izi ndege zitagira abadereva muri Ukraine
 Kirby ati: "Tehran ubu ifisemwo uruhara mu kuba iri ku rubuga be no mu gutanga ibirwanisho bigira ingaruka mbi ku basivire no ku bigo vya gisivire muri Ukraine”
 Avuga kandi ko Amerika “izokoresha uburyo bwose” mu “gushira ahabona, kuzibira no guhangana n’ibikorwa vya Irani vyo gutanga ibi birwanisho birwanya abanyagihugu ba Ukraine”
 Ukraine yabonye ko izi drones – canke indege zitagira abadereva (UAVs) – zakoreshejwe ku wa mbere, ko ari ibirwanisho vya Irani vyo mu bwoko bwa Shahed-136
 Zizwi ko ari iz’ “ubwiyahuzi” kuko zisambuka iyo zikoze igitero – zikaba zitiriwe ba badereva b’indege b’Abayapani bakoze ibikorwa vy’ubwiyahuzi mu ntambara ya kabiri y’isi yose
 Uburusiya bwakoresheje izi drones n’ibisasu vya misire mu gutera ibibanza bikomakomeye muri Ukraine mu misi iheze, busambura hafi ica gatatu c’amasoko ntanganguvu kuva ku wa mbere w’indwi iheze
 Ibi vyatumye muri Ukraine, ku ncuro ya mbere, haba amabwirizwa asaba abanyagihugu gukoresha umuyagankuba muke ejo ku wa kane
 Ubwongereza bwatangaje ibihano ku bajenerali batatu ba Irani hamwe n’uruganda ruhingura ibirwanisho kubera izi drones za Irani zakoreshejwe n’Uburusiya mu gutera Ukraine
 Umunyamabanga w’Ubwongereza ajejwe imigenderanire James Cleverly  yagirije abo bafatiwe ibihano “gukokeza intambara” no kwikika inyuma y’ibitero “vy’agahomerabunwa” vya Moscou
 Muri abo bafatiwe ibihano harimwo umukuru w’igisirikare ca Irani Jenerali-Majoro Mohammad Hossein Bagheri, hamwe kandi n’uruganda ruhingura drone ruzwi nka Shahed Aviation Industries
 Hagati aho, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine yagirije Moscou gutega ibibombe ku rugomero rukomeye mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Mu gihe urugomero rw’umuyagankuba rwa Kakhovka rwokwononekara cane, ibisagara 80 bishobora guterwa n’imyizurira, mbere n’ikigo ca nikleyeri ca Zaporizhzhia kikabura amazi yo guhoza, nk’uko Zelensky abivuga
 Bishobora kandi gutuma ubumanuko bwose bwa Ukraine, harimwo na Crimea, bubura amazi
 Ku wa gatatu, umurwi w’abahinga wo ku kigo cigisha ibijanye n’intambara, Institute for the Study of War, bavuze ko Moscou ishobora kuba iriko irategura igitero kuri uru rugomero igaca icegeka kuri Ukraine, yizeye ko umwuzurira wokwaduka woha akaryo keza ingabo z’Uburusiya ko kuva mu turere tw’intara ya Kherson ata nkomanzi
 Uru rugomero rupima ibirometero 70 rukaba ruri mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Kherson
 Uburusiya buriko burahungisha abasivire bubakura mu turere twa Kherson bugenzura, mu gihe bwiteze igitero gikomeye ca Ukraine mu ntumbero yo kwisubiza iki gisagara

Na Ciaran Varley BBC Sport Lionel Messi nta nkeka, ni we mukinyi rurangiranwa mu mupira w’amaguru
 Ku myaka 35, uyu musatirizi wa Argentina amaze gutsindira hafi ubushimwe bwose muri uru rukino
 Yatsindiye Umupira w’Inzahabu (Ballon d'Or) – agashimwe gahabwa umukinyi wa mbere mwiza kw’isi – aho yaciye umuhigo mu kugatsindira incuro indwi, yongera atsindira agashimwe ka FIFA  k’umukinyi mwiza ku ruhande rw’abagabo rimwe
 Mu bundi bushimwe harimwo ibikombe bine vy’ihiganwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere iwabo (Ligue des Champions/ Champions League), atsindira ibikombe 11 vy’ihiganwa ryo mu gihugu, yongera atsindira igikombe c’ihiganwa rya Amerika (Copa America) mu 2021
  Ico abuze conyene
 Ni igikombe c’isi yose
 Hagati aho ariko, tuzi bike cane ku bijanye n’uyu muntu w’imbaga ntoya ariko atera akukuruka
 Mw’ireresi nshasha y’isaha yakorewe BBC, benshi mu bahoranye nawe mu murwi be n’abakinyi bigeze guhangana nawe, hamwe kandi n’abanyamakuru bakoze amakuru kuri we, barinjira muri kino gitangaza, ari we Messi
 Ng’ibi bike mu vyo twokuramwo
 Messi yinjiye mw’ishure ry’umupira w’amaguru rya Barcelona, La Masia, afise imyaka 13
 Iri ni ishure ry’umupira w’amaguru ryasohoye ibihangange nka Xavi, Andres Iniesta, Gerard Pique na Cesc Fabregas
 Fabregas yahoze akina hagati muri Barcelona, Arsenal na Chelsea avuga ko ikintu ca mbere yabonye ku muyabaga Messi  ni uko “yari umwana muto, atavuga, yari afise isoni nyinshi”
 Isoni ni ikintu kiguma kigaruka cane, aho umunyamakuru w’ikinyamakuru Guardian, Jonathan Wilson, avuga ko Messi yahora yihindurira mu gasimbaryango (corridor) hakwinjira mu vyumba vyo kwihinduriramwo
 Fabregas abandanya asigura ingene uyu muyabaga yitonda cane yatangaje abantu bose mu myimenyerezo
 Avuga ati: "Mu myimenyerezo ya mbere twagiranye na Leo, nakina cane ku ruhande rwo hagati amaja inyuma (milieu défensif /defensive midfielder), kandi tukaba twahura turi umwe kuri umwe
 "Mu mutwe iwanje, nibaza ko ndamwaka umupira ata ngorane kuko nakunda gukinira hasi kandi nkunda 'tackle', ariko rero mbona afise umuvuduko udasanzwe
 Naratangaye, kuko ndibuka nikubise hasi ngo ndawumwake ariko aransiga aca arinjiza”
 Fabregas avuga ko, kuva ico gihe, yaciye abona ko “dukwiye kwitwararika cane uyu muhungu”
 Imbere y’uko ava mu murwi mu 2021, Messi yafashije Barcelona gutsindira ihiganwa rya La Liga incuro cumi, ibikombe bine vya Ligue des Champions, ibikombe indwi vya Copa del Rey hamwe n’ibikombe umunani vya super coupes muri Espagne
 Messi mu kwimukira muri Barcelona vyasigura impinduka zikomeye ku muryango wiwe
 Umunyamakuru Guillem Balague yanditse igitabo ndangakahise kuri Messi, arasigura ingene vyamugoye gufata ingingo
 Nk’uko abisigura, inyuma y’amezi atandatu ashitse muri Barcelona, abavyeyi ba Messi batumyeko inama y’umuryango
 Mushikiwe Maria, ntihari hamuguye neza, mu gihe mwenewabo nawe Matias yari afise umukunzi yasize i Rosario
 Balague ati: "Cari igihe co gufata ingingo, ‘tugume i Barcelona canke dusubire i Rosario'? “Bicaye ku meza bamubaza bati, 'Leo, wipfuza gukora iki?' Leo avuga ati, 'Nshaka gutera imbere
 Nshaka kuba muri Barcelona, nshaka kuba umukinyi rurangiranwa'
" Balague asigura ko ico Messi atari yabwiwe zari inkurikizi z’ibi – nyina wiwe yategerezwa gusubiza mushikiwe na benewabo babiri i Rosario hanyuma se wiwe akagumana nawe
 Balague ati: " Akenshi, yarinjira mu cumba ciwe agashira umutwe munsi y’umusego akarira
 "Yakora ivyo kugira ngo se wiwe ntamwumve
 Afise myaka 14 gushika kuri 15, niho yabona ko, kubera ingingo yiwe, yategerezwa kubitahura”
 Rio Ferdinand yagize igihamana kibi co guhura na Lionel Messi n’abandi bakinyi ba Pep Guardiola bari bateye ubwoba muri Barcelona mu rukino rwa nyuma rwa Ligue des Champions, atari incuro imwe gusa, ariko zibiri
 Manchester United yahuye n’aba ba Catalans mu 2009 hanyuma mu 2011 – aho hompi itsindwa
 Mu 2009, Barcelona yatsinze 2-0 aho Messi yinjije igitsindo kigira kabiri ciza cane n’umutwe
 Ferdinand yahushije umupira wari utewe na Xavi imbere y’igori
 Ferdinand  ati: "Messi yinjije n’umutwe, bose wamengo bambaza ngo ‘raba ingene ungana, n’ingene angana
 Nta vyinshi yinjije nk’ivyo kuva atanguye gukina, ariko yabikoze mu gihe kidasanzwe”
 Messi yarinjije kandi yongera aba umukinyi w’urukino (man of the match) mu rukino rwa nyuma rwa 2011 Barcelona yatsinze 3-1
 "Messi wamengo, nta guhuza amaso, nta kintu na kimwe, ari ukwiwe, nta n’uko akwegereye, hanyuma ubwo nyene ukaza wumva ng’uyo, ‘aragusetse’
 Iryo joro baratwishe pe”
 Mu kiringo cose amaze akina umupira, haba neza canke nabi, yagiye agereranywa n’ikindi gihangange ca Argentina: Diego Maradona
 Iyi reresi yerekana ingene Messi atorohewe mu kwikorera umuzigo w’iri gereranya
 Maradona yabaye ntibagiranwa igihe atsindira igikombe c’isi yose mu 1986
 Messi yamenyekanye mu rukino rwa nyuma rw’igikombe c’isi yose mu 2014 akaba yari amaze gukina inkino za nyuma za Copa Amerika ariko aho hose nta gikombe yari bwatsindire igihugu ciwe gushika mu 2021 aho batahukaniye igikombe ca Copa Amerika
 N’aho hari ibintu bisa mu buhinga bwabo bwo gukina, umunyamakuru wa Guardian Marcela Mora y Araujo arerekana ubudasa mu nyifato hagati ya Messi na Maradona
 Avuga ati: "Maradona yamenyekanye cane kubera impari
 Nibaza ko Messi ateye imbere gusumba, aho kudugira ku mpari, yadugiye ku kwifatanya n'abandi
 Messi akeneye kuba mu murwi umeze neza, kandi ukorera hamwe”
 Uwundi mukinyi Messi akunze kugereranywako igihe cose ni Cristiano Ronaldo
 Be na we, bamaze imyaka irenga cumi bahurira ku bushimwe nyamukuru hafi bwose mu mupira w’amaguru
 Messi afise Ballon d'Or indwi, mu gihe Ronaldo afise zitanu, akaba kandi afise ibikombe vya Ligue des Champions bine Ronaldo nawe afise bitanu
 Ariko none ubu bushamirane si bumwe bukokezwa n'abakora imyihwezo, abanyamakuru n'abafana? Xavi, yahoze akinana na Messi abona ko ivyo ari ukuri
 Ati: "Cristiano yamuteye intege zo kuba umukinyi rurangiranwa
 "Kumbure Cristiano na Leo bashobora kutavyemera uko
 Ariko ndazi neza ko bagumye barabana ku kajisho
 Iyo uriko urahiganwa, uba ushaka kuba uwa mbere”

Na Patience Atuhaire B﻿BC News, Kampala Sentare  yo muri Uganda yaciriye umuntu adandaza amasenge y’inzovu gupfungwa ubuzima bwiwe bwose – igihano ca mbere kinini  ku caha nk’ico muri kahise k’ico gihugu
 Itegeko rishasha ryemejwe mu 2019 ryakajije ibihano ku bantu bakora uruhigi rutemewe n’amategeko canke bakora urudandazwa rw’inyamaswa zigeramiwe no guhona
 Pascal Ochiba  yafashwe muri Nzero uyu mwaka afise ibimanyu bibiri vy’amasenge y’inzovu, bipima hafi 10kg
 Umucamanza yavuze ko Ochiba, asanzwe yari amaze kwagirwa n’icaha nk’ico muri kahise, akwiye umunyororo w’ubuzima bwose kugira muri kazoza inyamaswa zikingirwe
 Mu gusoma urwo rubanza, umukuru wa sentare  y’igihugu idasanzwe ijejwe inyamaswa, Gladys Kamasanyu, yavuze ko “ivyaha vyo  kutunga mu buryo butemewe n’amategeko ubwoko bukingiwe bisigaye ari vyinshi kandi hakenewe ko bituzwa”, nk’uko biri mw’itangazo ry’urwego rushinzwe inyamaswa muri Uganda (Uganda Wildlife Authority)
 Umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa wa UWA Sam Mwandha  yavuze ati: “Iki ni ikintu gikomeye cane mu rugamba rwacu rwo kurwanya urudandazwa rw’inyamaswa rutemewe n’amategeko
” Mu 2020, umuhigi yishe inguge izwi nka Rafiki yahanishijwe imyaka 11 y’umunyororo
 Muri Nyakanga/Nzeri uyu mwaka, abagabo babiri umwe umwe yahanishijwe gupfungwa imyaka umunani ku caha co kwica intare zitandatu zidakunze kuboneka zo mu bwoko bwurira ibiti
 Mu mashamba ya Uganda hahurwa ko hasigaye inzovu 7
900 harimwo izo mu mashamba (forêts) n’izo mu gahinga (savane)
 Ishirahamwe ryo kubungabunga ibibaho (Union for Conservation of Nature) zishira izo mu mashamba mu zigeramiwe cane mu gihe izo mu gahinga zishirwa mu zigeramiwe
 Igitigiri c’inzovu muri ico gihugu cagumye ciyongera kuva mu myaka ya 1990
 Ariko ivyo bikoko n’ubu biracageramiwe n’abantu babihiga kandi babicuruza bitemewe n’amategeko
 Ochiba yari amaze guphungwa muri kahise – mu 2017 – igihe yafatanwa ibimanyu bine  vy’amasenge y’inzovu  hamwe n’urushato rw’igikoko bita Okapi
 Okapi, giteye bwa mparage, n’igikoko kitagwiriye kiba gusa mu mashamba ya Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo ihana urubibe na Uganda

N﻿a Steve Rosenberg Umwanditsi mukuru ku Burusiya Igitsure kuri Vladimir Putin kibandanya ciyongera
 “Igikorwa ca gisirikare  kidasanzwe” ciwe ntikiriko kiragenda uko categuwe
 Uburusiya buriko buratakaza ubutaka bwari bwariguriye kubera ibitero vyo kwivuna vya Ukraine
 Ni mu gihe uturere tw’Uburusiya duhana urubibe na Ukraine tubandanya ducucagirwa amabombe
 Hejuru y’ibi, akamo ka Kremlin ko mu kwezi guheze ko kwinjiza izindi ngabo kateje impungenge mu Barusiya
 None inyishu ya Putin yoba ari iyahe?  Ntabwo ari “Mbabarira, narakoze ikosa rikomeye mu gutera Ukraine”
 Ahubwo ni ugukomeza umutekano
 Aho si mu turere twigaruriwe n’Uburusiya muri Ukraine, ahubwo ni mu gihugu cose
 Ariko arakaza akagozi
 Mw’itegeko-bwirizwa rya Kremlin, Vladimir Putin yashizeho amategeko ya gisirikare muri za ntara zine za Ukraine avuga ko yihagiye: Luhansk, Donetsk, Zaporizhzhia na Kherson
 Ntibiboneka neza akarusho bizozana, nimba kahari: iri tegeko ntirizotuma ingabo za Ukraine zishira ibirwanisho hasi
 Kyiv yariyemeje kubohoza ubutaka yatakaje
 Ariko kandi umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yakomeje umutekano mu gihugu cose, mu gushiranga ingero zitatu zitandukanye z’umutekano
 Muri izo ntara zihana urubibe na Ukraine, izo ni nka Belgorod, Bryansk, Krasnodar na Rostov, hamwe kandi no mu karere ka Crimea yigaruriye, “ingingo ziciriye hagati na hagati” zatangajwe
 Muri zo harimwo kwongereza umutekano: iri tegeko-bwirizwa ritegekanya kandi kugabanya uruja n’uruza rw’amamodoka, hamwe no kwinjira no gusohoka muri izi ntara
 Urugero rukurikira ni “ukumera magabo gusumba”
 Aha ni mu ntara zo hagati no mu bumanuko bw’Uburusiya, harimwo na Moscou
 Iri tegeko rya perezida riravugamwo “ugusaka amamodoka no kugabanya uruja n’uruza rwayo”, hamwe kandi no “gukomeza umutekano w’abanyagihugu”
 Mu butumwa yacishije ku mbuga hwaniro,  umukuru w’igisagara ca Moscou Sergei Sobyanin yagerageje guhumuriza abanyagihugu ba Moscou ko ata  “ngingo zizoza zibabuza ubuzima busanzwe”
 Urugero rutoya rw’izi ngingo rwerekeye utundi turere dusigaye tw’igihugu (aha no nko mu buraruko bw’Uburusiya, Siberia hamwe no mu buseruko bw’igihugu)
 Mu ntumbero yo gushira mu ngiro itegeko rya Perezida Putin, ba buramatari bose bategetswe gushinga “ivyicaro bikuru”
