N﻿a Steve Rosenberg Umwanditsi mukuru mu gisata c'Ikirusiya, i Moscow Iki ni ikibazo tumaze igihe kitari gito tubaza, n’imbere y’uko Uburusiya butera Ukraine
 Vladimir Putin yoba yiyumvira iki agategura iki? Ariko reka mbe ndabibamenyesha
 Nta sindagura
 Kandi sinavuganye na Putin
 Uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu ca Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika George W Bush igihe kimwe niho yigeze kuvuga ko yaravye Vladimir Putin mu maso aca abona akari ku mutima wiwe
 Raba ingene vyarangiye neza mu migenderanire hagati y’Uburusiya n’Uburengero
 Rero, kwinjira mu mutwe w’uyu mutegetsi wa Kremlin si igikorwa coroshe
 Ariko ni vyiza kugerageza
 Kumbure iki gihe nico gikomeye co kugerageza gusumba ibindi vyose, dufatiye kw’ikangisha riheruka kugirwa na Moscou ku bigwanisho nikleyeri
 Nta gukekeranya cane ko umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya ubu atorohewe
 Ico yita “igikorwa ca gisirikare kidasanzwe” muri Ukraine ntikiriko kimugendera neza
 Cari citezwe kumara imisi mike
 Ariko ubu turi mu mezi hafi umunani kandi nta kimenyetso ko kigiye kurangira
 Kremlin iremera ko yatakaje “bikomeye”; mu ndwi nkeya za vuba, igisirikare c’Uburusiya cagiye gitakaza ubutaka cari carigaruriye muri Ukraine
 Mu ntumbero yo kwongereza igitigiri c’ingabo, mu kwezi guheze Perezida Putin yateye akamo ko guhamagaza ingabo, ico yahora avuga ashimitse ko atari gukora
 Ni mu gihe ibihano bibandanya bigira ingaruka mbi ku butunzi bw’Uburusiya
 Reka tugaruke ku coba kiri mu mutwe wa Putin
 Ubwo yoba yibaza ko yihenze cane? Ko ingingo yo gutera Ukraine ryabaye ikosa rikomeye? Ntuhave uvyemeza gutyo
 Konstantin Remchukov, umwanditsi mukuru akongera akaba nyene ikinyamakuru co mu Burusiya Nezavisimaya Gazeta, avuga ati: "Ivyo Putin yiyumvira ni vyo vyerekana ingene ibintu bimeze muri ino ntambara”
 "Ni umutegetsi atwaza umukazo igihugu rutura ca nikleyeri
 Ni umutegetsi atavuguruzwa muri kino gihugu
 Arafise ivyiyumviro n’ibintu bikomeye yemera bimusarisha
 Yatanguye kwemeza ko ari ku nyungu zo kubaho
 Atari kuri we gusa
 Ariko kuri kazoza k’Uburusiya”
 Mu gihe ino ntambara yoba ari iyo kurwanira ukubaho kw’igihugu, Putin yoba yiteguye gute kuyitsinda? Mu mezi ya vuba, abategetsi b’Uburusiya (na Putin we nyene ubwiwe arimwo) bagiye bumvikana mu buryo budatomoye berekana ko uyu mukuru wa Kremlin ashobora kuba yiteguriye gukoresha ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri muri ino ntambara
 Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika abwira CNN ati: "Sinibaza ko azohava abikoresha
 Ariko nibaza ko kubona avuga ibintu nk’ibi ko ata mutima agira”
 Amabombe y’urutavanako yacucagiwe mu gihugu cose mu ndwi iheze yerekana ko nibura Kremlin yiteguye kwunyura ibintu hagati y'Ubususiya na Ukraine
 N'uburengero nyene? Grigory Yavlinsky, inararibonye muri poritike nk’uwigenga, avuga ati: "Ariko aragerageza kwirinda ko hatoba ugutana mu mitwe amaso mu yandi n’Uburengero, ariko akaba anavyiteguriye”
 "Mfise ubwoba ko hohava haduka intambara ya nikleyeri
 Hanyuma ubwa kabiri, ntinya intambara itagira iherezo”
 Ariko "intambara itagira iherezo" isaba uburyo butagira iherezo
 Iki ni ikintu Uburusiya busa n’ubudafise
 Igihuhusi c’ibisasu vya misire vyacucagiwe ku bisagara vya Ukrane ni ukwerekana inguvu zidasanzwe, ariko none Moscou yobibandanya mu gihe kingana iki? Remchukov ati: "None woshobora kubandanya utera izi misire mu kiringo c’imisi, c’amayinga, c’amezi? Abahinga benshi bafise amakenga ko tutoba dufise misire zikwiye
 "Hanyuma kandi, turavye ku ruhande rwa gisirikare, nta n’umwe gushika ubu arerekana icoba ikimenyetso kirengeye vyose c’intsinzi [y’Uburusiya]? Ni ikihe kimenyetso c’intsinzi? Mu 1945 cabaye ibendera hejuru ya Berlin
 None ubu icokwerekana intsinzi ni igiki? [Ibendera] hejuru ya Kyiv? Hejuru ya Kherson? Hejuru ya Kharkiv? Si nzi
 Nta n’umwe abizi”
 Nta n’uwuzi nimba na Vladimir Putin we nyene ubwiwe abizi
 Mu kwa kabiri, intumbero ya Kremlin  yasa n’ugutsinda Ukraine vuba bwango, hanyuma uyu mubanyi w’Uburusiya agasubira mu muryango w’ibihugu bicuditse na Moscou ata ntambara ndende ihabaye
 Aha yaharuye nabi
 Uretse ko atiyumviriye ko igisirikare ca Ukrane n’abanyagihugu bayo bari biyemeje kurwanira igihugu cabo gushika ku ka nyuma, ntiyibaza ko igisirikare cayo cari gifise uburyo bwo guhangana n’Uburusiya
 None ubu yoba yiyumvira iki? Ubwo ubu Vladimir Putin yoba  afise integuro yo gutsimbataza igenzura ry’ubutaka bwa Ukraine avuga ko aherutse kwihagira hanyuma agahagarika intambara? Canke ubwo yoba yariyemeje kubandanya asatira gushika Ukraine yose ayigarukanye mu ruhongore rw’ibihugu bigenzurwa na Kremlin? Mu ndwi iheze, Dmitry Medvedev  yahoze arongoye Uburusiya yanditse ati: "Igihugu ca Ukraine, uravye ukungene cubatse  ubu


kizokwama ari intambamyi ikomeye ku Burusiya
 Mbona ko intego y’ibikorwa vyacu vya kazoza yoba ugusenyura burundu ubutegetsi bwa poritike bwa Ukraine”
 Mu gihe amajambo ya Medvedev ari yo yoba ari mu mutwe wa Putin, aha rero mwitege intambara ndende cane kandi izosesekamwo amaraso menshi
 Ariko, vyanka bikunda, ivyo Putin akora hanze biriko bigira ingaruka mu gihugu
  Kuva mu myaka itari mike, Kremlin yarubatse ishusho ya Putin nka "Mr Stability" (ni ukuvuga “Umugabo-buragamo"), ihimiriza Abarusiya kwizera ko igihe cose azoba arongoye igihugu ko bazoba bari mu mutekano utagira agahonzi
 Ubu biragoye kwumvisha abantu ko ari vyo
 Remchukov ati: "Amasezerano yari hagati ya Putin n’abanyagihugu yari ‘Ndagukingira’
 "Mu kiringo c’imyaka itari mike, icivugo nyamukuru cari ‘ukubona kure’
 None ukwo kubona kure muri kino gihe ni ukuhe? Ico carataye igihe
 Nta kintu na kimwe co kwizera muri kazoza
 Uno musi abanyamakuru banje ntibazi nimba badashika muhira basanga urwandiko rubahamagarira kwinjira mu gisirikare”
 Ingingo ya Vladimir Putin yo gutera Ukraine yatangaje benshi
 Ariko Yavlinsky ntarimwo
 Yavlinsky  ati: "Nibaza ko [Putin] yamaze igihe yitegurira iyo nzira – umwaka ku mwaka yariko yubaka ivyo turimwo ubu”
 "Akarorero, gusambura ibinyamakuru vyingenga
 Ivyo yabitanguye mu 2001
 Gusambura igisata c’abikorera utwabo
 Yabitanguye mu 2003
 Hanyuma mu 2014 ivyabaye muri Crimea na Donbas
 Umuntu atabibona ni uko yari impumyi
 "Ingorane z’Uburusiya ni intwaro yacu
 Intwaro yashinzwe hano ikarema uyu muntu  [nka Putin]
 Ikibazo c’uruhara rw’Uburengero mu gushinga iyi ntwaro ni ikibazo gikomeye cane
 "Ikibazo ni uko iyi ntwaro itaremye abantu
 Hari abantu benshi cane b’intungane mu Burusiya
 Ariko mu bantu nta gatima ko guharanira uburenganzira  kahari
 Nico gituma Uburusiya bunanirwa kwihagararako”

Agahinda n’umubabaro mu Bufaransa vyatewe n’igandagurwa ry’umwana w’umukobwa w’imyaka 12 yatowe yatawe mu gisandugu ca plastiki i Paris vyavuyemwo ikibazo ca poritike gishingiye ku biranga uwikekwa nk’umwimukira
 Ikiziga ca Lola catowe ku wa gatanu w’indwi iheze hanze mu rugo imbere y’urupangu yabamwo
 Umugore w’imyaka 24 yatawe mu gasho yiketsweko ubwicanyi, ugufata ku nguvu n’iyica rubozo
 Vyagiye kuboneka kandi ko ari umwimukira akomoka muri Algeria yari asanzwe yategetswe kuva mu Bufaransa
 Inyuma y’akanya gato, Perezida Emmanuel Macron yabonanye n’abavyeyi b’uyu mukobwa ku kirimba Élysée (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu) ejo ku wa kabiri aca abemerera kubafata mu mugongo, abatavuga rumwe muri poritike bakagiriza reta ko batafashije umuryango
 Mw’ikoraniro ry’inama nshingamateka ritari ryoroshe, Marine Le Pen umukuru w’umugambwe Front National ariyamiriza poritike “ataco imaze” ya reta ku vyerekeye abimukira
 Avuga ati: "Uwikekwa gukora iki caha c’ubugome ntiyategerezwa kuba hano mu gihugu cacu; ni igiki kibabujije guhagurukira iki kibazo c’abimukira bo mu kinyegero batagenzurwa”? Umushikiranganji wa mbere Elisabeth Borne yamusavye “kwerekana ubwitonzi” akubahiriza umuryango uri mu mubabaro utewe no kubura Lola, akavuga ati:  "Reka duhe akaryo igipolisi n’ubutungane bakore akazi kabo”
 Lola yazimiye ku wa gatanu uheze vyanse ko ashika muhira avuye kw’ishure, atari na kure, muri district ya 19 mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw’umugwa mukuru Paris
 Ku kagoroba, niho ikiziga ciwe catorwa mu gisandugu ca plastiki
 Isuzuma ryakozwe inyuma y’urupfu ryasanze yagize ibibazo vyo kubura impemu “afise n’ibimenyetso vy’umuntu yanizwe”
 Basanze kandi afise ibiguma mu maso, mu mugongo no kw’izosi ariko ibi sivyo vyatumye apfa
 Kubera se wiwe ari we ajejwe iyo nyubakwa, yaciye arondera amashusho yafashwe na CCTV (camera zo gucungera uruja n’uzura) yerekana uwikekwa gukora iri bara Dahbia B, ari kumwe n’umukobwa wiwe mu cumba c’amagorofa ku muhingamo wo ku wa gatanu
 Umugabo w’imyaka 43 yagirijwe ko yafashije mu kunyegeza ikiziga c’uyu mukobwa
 Abatavuga rumwe na reta baciye bihutira kwerekana ko Dahbia B yari abaye mu gihugu bidaciye mu mategeko
 Ubwa mbere yabanje guhagarikwa ku kibuga c’indege mu Bufaransa ku wa 20 z’ukwa munani kubera uruhusha rwo kuba mu gihugu rwari rwarataye igihe
 Yari yinjiye mu Bufaransa biciye mu mategeko nk’umunyeshuri imyaka itandatu iheze
 Dahbia B yari yategetswe kuva mu Bufaransa mu kiringo kitarenga ukwezi, kw’itegeko ryitwa OQTF (obligation de quitter le territoire français/itegeko ryo kuva ku butaka bw’Ubufaransa)
 N’aho amategeko amwe amwe ategerezwa gushirwa mu ngiro mu buryo bwihuse, Dahbia B nta kintu cerekana ko yahora akora ivyaha, bituma adashirwa mu gasho
 Amategeko ya OQTF aravugwa cane kubera rimwe kw’icumi ari yo ashirwa mu ngiro, abanya-Algeria bakaba bari mu bantu bafatwa ko bayahonyanga
 Umushikiranganji w’intwaro yo hagati Gérald Darmanin yasavye abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi bo ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku vya kera kwiyumvira ku nkurikizi y’amajambo bakoresha
 Ni inyuma y’aho uwigeze kwiyamamariza ikibanza c’umukuru w’igihugu kuri urwo ruhande Éric Zemmour avuze ko iki caha ari "Francocide", ni ukuvuga igandagurwa ry’umufaransa
 Uyu mushikiranganji yabwiye radiyo RTL, ko habuzemwo ubwitonzi na butoya mu mvugo za poritike

 Eka n’abandi banyaporitike bo kuri uru ruhande baranegura reta, aho umushingamateka wo ku ruhande rw’abarepubulika Éric Pauget yabwiye umushikiranganji w’ubutungane ko "Lola yishwe kubera mutirukanye uyu munyamahanga”
 Haracari igipfungu ku catumye haba ubu bwicanyi, uwuburanira uwikekwa akaba yiyamiriza ibihuha bitari bike biriko birazunguruka mu gihugu
 Umushikirizamanza wa repubulika i Paris igiharuro rimwe n’ubusa vyari vyanditswe musi y’ikirenge ca nyakwigendera, ariko ntibavuga igituma
 Kimwe mu vyoba vyatumye haba ubu bwicanyi nk’uko amasoko yabibwiye abakora amatohoza ni imishamirano hagati y’uwufata iya mbere mu bikekwa na nyina wa Lola
 Dahbia B yari asanzwe aba mu rupangu rumwe na mwenewabo ariko igihe yasaba uruhusha rwo kwinjira mu rupangu, nyina wa Lola yaramwankiye
 Uwikekwa apfungiwe ukwa wenyene mw’ibohero rya Fresnes, mu bumanuko bwa Paris
 Amakuru avuga ko yari amaze imyaka itari mike akorerwa ihohotera ryo mu rugo akaba agiye gukorerwa ibipimo vyo mu mutwe
 Imyiyerekano y’agacerere mu kwibuka Lola yahagaritswe kuri uno wa gatatu bisabwe n’umuryango
 Hagati aho, yitezwe kuba ku musi ukurikira, aho abanyaporitike batari bake bo ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku vya kera bitezwe kuyitabira

P﻿rezida wa Uganda Yoweri Museveni yavuze ko umuhungu wiwe, Gen Muhoozi Kainerugaba, atazosubira  kugira ico avuze ku vyerekeye reta kuri Twitter
 I﻿vyo bishitse inyuma y'amajambo menshi yaciye ku mbuga hwaniro mu ndwi zibiri ziheze aho Gen Kainerugaba, w'imyaka 48, yanditse kuri Twitter ivyerekeye gutera igihugu kibanyi ca Kenya, no kwigarurira umugwa mukuru waco, Nairobi,  mu ndwi zitarenga zibiri
 I﻿nyuma y'aho, prezida Museveni yarasavye imbabazi abanya-Kenya kuri izo tweets
 K﻿u musi wa mbere, prezida Museveni yabwiye imboneshakure yo  muri Uganda ati: "Azova kuri Twitter
 Twarabiganiriye
 Twitter si co kibazo
 Ikibazo n'ivyo wandikako
" Y﻿ongeyeko ati: "Kuvuga ivyerekeye ibindi bihugu no kugira aho yegamiye muri politike ya Uganda n'ibintu adategerezwa gukora kandi atazosubira gukora
" U﻿wo mutegetsi amaze imyaka myinshi ku butegetsi yavuze ko umuhungu wiwe afise uburenganzira bwo kwandika ivyerekeye "inkino canke ibindi bidateza impari"
 U﻿bushikiranganji bw'imigenderanire ya Uganda n'amakungu ntibwafashe nko gufyina, inyuma y'aho umuhungu wa prezida ateburiye ku kwigarurira Kenya ku ma Tweets atangaje yanditse
 Mw'itangazo ryo gusukamwo mabisi, reta ya Uganda yavuze ko yishimiye "imigenderanire ikomeye dusanzwe dufitaniye" n'"umuvukanyi w'umubanyi" Kenya kandi ko ata bikorwa vy'imigenderanire birangurirwa ku mbunga hwaniro
 A﻿ta gukekeranya, muri reta ya Uganda ntibishimiye urwenya rw'umuhungu mukuru wa prezida Yoweri Museveni, Gen Muhoozi Kainerugaba, n'aho bamwe bavuga ko ariko arategurwa ngo asubirire se wiwe w'imyaka 78
 Si ubwa mbere Tweets ziwe zitera impari ariko izi zerekeye kwigarurira Kenya bisa n'uko zarengeje urugero

Ukraine yagiriza Uburusiya ko bukoresha indege “z’ubwiyahuzi” (kamikaze) zo mu bwoko bwa drones (indege zitagira abadereva) mu gutera ibibanza vya gisivire i Kyiv
 Izi ndege ziremeka amabombe aturika iyo akoze ku kintu, agasambura izi drones mu guturika kwayo
 Bizwi ko kuva hagati mu kw’icenda, Uburusiya buriko bukoresha drone yo mu bwoko bwa Shahed-136 yatanzwe na Irani mu ntambara yabwo muri Ukraine
 Iyi ndege izwi kandi n’Uburusiya kw’izina rya Geranium-2 ifise ibibombe ku kizuruzuru cayo ikaba izwi ko ibanza gukizura ikibanza yarungitsweko imbere y’uko ihabwa uburenganzira bwo kugiseka
 Shahed-136 ifise ibaba ry’imetero zababa 2,5 kandi bifise kugorana ko ibonwa na vya vyuma bicungera ikirere (radars)
 Ntibizwi neza igitigiri Uburusiya bufise, ariko Amerika ivuga ko Irani yateguye kuburungikira amajana n’amajana
 Irani irahakana ibi
 Uburusiya bwatanguye kuvugwa ko bwakoresheje drone yo mu bwoko bwa Shahed-136 ku ncuro ya mbere ku wa 13 z’ukw’icenda, mu gutera ibibanza biri hafi ya Kupiansk, igisagara kiri mu ntara ya Kharkiv iri mu buseruko bw’igihugu
 Inyuma y’igihe muri uko kwezi nyene, yakoreshejwe mu bitero vyakozwe mu bumanuko
 Ibisigarira vy’izi drones vyagiye gutorwa i Odesa na Mykolaiv
 Mu kw’icumi, drones za Shahed-136 zaguye mu turere dutuwemwo n’abasivire mu gisagara ca Bila Tserkva, mu bumanuko bwa Kyiv
 Uburusiya bushobora kuba buriko bukoresha izi drones hagukoresha ibisasu vya misire kubera zisa n’izizimbutse – ku giciro cababa amadorari 20
000 ya Amerika imwe imwe
 Ingabo za Ukraine zikoresha misire zikorora indege be n’ubuhinga bwo kuyovya mu ntumbero yo kugerageza kumanura izi drones
 Mu ntango z’uku kw’icumi, ingabo za Ukraine zavuze ko zakoroye 60% za drone zose zo mu bwoko bwa Shahed-136 zinjiye mu gihugu
 Justin Crump , umuhinga mu vya gisirikare, yabwiye BBC ati: "Zigendera hafi kandi ushobora kuzirungika ica rimwe ari nyinshi
 "Iri segenya rya drones ntiryoroshe kurwanya ukoresheje ubuhinga bwo gucungera ikirere”
 Ntibiramenyekana neza nimba Ukraine yoba imaze gukoresha izi ndege, ariko abahinga bemeza ko zishobora kuba zarakoreshejwe mu bitero biheruka ku kirindiro c’ingabo z’Uburusiya mu burengero bwa Crimea, ku kirindiro c’ingabo zirwanira mu kirere hafi ya Sevastopol, be no ku mato yo ku kivuko ca Sevastopol
 Dr Marina Miron, umushakashatsi kw’ishure kaminuza King's College London, avuga ati: "Uravye ibiturika muri bino bitero, ni bito cane
 Nibaza ko izi ari drones zahinguwe n’abacuzi, zikambikwako n’ibiturika”
 Drone nyamukuru y’igisirikare ca Ukraine ni Bayraktar TB2 yakozwe na Turukiya
 Ni indege ntoya, ifise amacameras kandi ishobora kwambikwako amabombe
 Intambara igitangura, Ukraine yari ifise “izidashika 50”, nk’uko bivugwa na Dr Jack Watling wo mu kigo c’abahinga Royal United Services Institute (Rusi)
 Amerika ivuga ko iriko irarungikira Ukraine drones 700 zo mu bwoko buzwi nka Switchblade, nazo nyene zikaba ari drones z’ubwiyahuzi
 Uburusiya bukoresha kandi drone "ntoya, iri hasi cane” yo mu bwoko bwa Orlan-10, ifise camera kandi ishobora kwikorera amabombe matomato
 Ku mpande zompi – Uburusiya na Ukraine – drones zabaye kirumara mu kubona aho umwansi aherereye no gutera vya muzinga
 Dr Watling ati: "Ingabo z’Uburusiya zishobora gukoresha iminota hagati y’itatu na cumi mu gushikana inkoho ku kibanza cabonywe na Orlan-10 kugira zihangane n’umwansi”
 Igitero gishobora gufata iminota 20-30 kugira kibe
 Dr Marina Miron avuga ko drones zafashije Ukraine kwagura akarere k’ingabo
 Mu ndwi nkeya za mbere z’iyi ntambara, drones za Ukraine zo mu bwoko bwa Bayraktar zarahayagizwa cane
 Dr Miron  ati: "Zerekanwa ziriko ziratera ibibanza bimwe bimwe nk’ahanyegeje ibirwanisho, kandi zaragize uruhara mu gusenyura ubwato bw’intambara Moskova”
 Ariko Bayraktar drone ndende kandi igenda bukebuke, Uburusiya bukaba bwarashoboye kuyituza bukoresheje ubuhinga bwabwo bwo gucungera ikirere
 Drones za gisirikare zirazimvye kugira uzisubirize - Bayraktar TB2 imwe gusa igurwa hafi imiriyoni zibiri z’amadorari y’Abanyamerika
 Rero, impande zompi – ariko cane cane Ukraine – zikoresha ntoya zikoreshwa mu bucuruzi, nka DJI Mavic 3, igurwa amadorari yababa $1
930
 Izi drones zo mu bucuruzi zishobora kwambikwako amabombe mato mato
 Ariko zikoreshwa cane cane mu guhiga umwansi no gukora ibitero
 Dr Miron  ati: "Ukraine ntinganya ibirwanisho n’Uburusiya
 Kugira ‘amaso mu kirere’ kugira ubone ibibanza ushobore no kubitera bisigura ko bashobora gukoresha neza ivyo bafise”
 Ariko drones z’ubucuruzi zifise ubushobozi buto cane ugereranije n’iza gisirikare
 Akarorero, DJI Mavic ishobora gushika ku birometero 30 gusa, ikaba ishobora kuguruka gushika ku minota 46 gusa
 Uburusiya bukoresha ubuhinga bwa elektroniki mu kuzirasa, nk’uko Dr Miron abivuga
 Avuga ati: "Ingabo z’Uburusiya zifise ibirwanisho vyo mu bwoko bwa Stupor bishobora kurasa  imishwarara”
 Ibi bituma drone idashobora kugenda ikoresheje ubuhinga bwa GPS, nk’uko abisigura
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya zirakoresha kandi n’ubuhinga buca ku ngurukanabumenyi, nka Aeroscope mu gutora no gukata itumatumanako hagati ya drones z’ubucuruzi n’abazikoresha
 Ubu buhinga bushobora gutuma drone ikoroka cane igasubira ku kirindiro, igashobora kuyibuza kurungika inkuru

Uburusiya bwahaye Ukraine impfungwa z’intambara zigizwe n’abagore 108, nayo ibuha impfungwa zabwo 110 yari ifise, nk’uko abategetsi ku mpande zompi babimenyesha
 Muri abo bagore, 37 bari bafashwe inyuma yo kwishikana inyuma y’imisi itari mike bugaraniwe muri rwa ruganda rwa Azovstal muri Mariupol rwari rugoswe gushika mu kwa gatanu
 Abarusiya bapfunguwe hafi bose ni abadereva b’amato y’ubucuruzi yafatiwe muri Ukraine
 Harimwo kandi n’abarwanyi bo mu murwi w’inyeshamba zishaka kwiyonkora zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya mu karere ka Donbas mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 Amasanamu yo ku murango yarasohowe yerekana aba bagore b’abanya-Ukraine burira amamodokari mu karere katamenyekanye mu nyuma berekanwa buhwibiriye bashitse mu karere kari muminwe ya reta mu ntara ya Zaporizhzhia iri mu bumanuko
 Aciye ku mbuga hwaniro, umukuru w’ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu vya Ukraine, Andriy Yermak, yaremeje ko abagore 108 barekuwe mu gikorwa co guhanahana impfungwa zose zigizwe n’abagore ku ncuro ya mbere
 Avuga ko harimwo abavyeyi n’abakobwa babo bari bafashwe bugwati
 Bose havuyemwo 12 bari abasirikare nk’uko abivuga
 Denis Pushilin, umutegetsi mukuru wo mu ntara ya Donetsk ishaka kwiyonkora kuri Ukraine ishigikiwe n’Uburusiya, aremeza iri hanahana ry’impfungwa, ariko akavuga ko impfungwa zibiri zahisemwo kwigumira mu Burusiya
 Kyiv ntaco iravuga kuri ibi
 Pushilin avuga ko izi mpfungwa zarekuwe na Ukraine zigizwe n’abadereva b’amato 80 hamwe n’abasirikare 30

Matt McGrath Umunyamakuru w'ibidukikije Amesenge (amenyo)  y’inzovu zishwe haraheze imyaka irenga 30 yongeye kuboneka mu yafashwe ubu vuba, nk’uko abahinga babivuga
 Ayo masenge yigeze kuba ari mu yafatanywe abakora urudandazwa rwayo rutemewe n’amategeko hanyuma aca yugaranirwa mu ma konteneri na reta y’Ubuurundi
 Muri ico cigwa, abashakashatsi bakoresheje ubuhinga bwa ADN/DNA  n’ubwa carbone bwo  gutora imyaka kugira berekane ko amwe muri ayo masenge yari yarugaranywe ubu ari mu minwe y’abakora urwo rudandazwa rwo mu kinyegero
 Reta y’Uburundi ntaco irishura ku busabe bwa BBC bwo kugira ico ibivuzeko
 Hagati ya 2007 na 2016, inzovu zishika 100
000 zarishwe zironderwako amasenge yazo mu bice bitandukanye vya Afrika
 Ico cigwa cakozwe ku bipimo vy’amasenge yafatiwe ahantu hane n’abajejwe kwubahiriza amategeko hagati ya 2017 na 2019
 Hakoreshejwe ubuhinga bwa carbone-14, abashakashatsi batoye ko menshi muri ayo masenge ari ayo inzovu  zari zishwe mu myaka itatu y’imbere y’aho
 Ariko, hari aho yafashwe bigaragara ko ari ayo inzovu zari zimaze imyaka 30 zishwe
 Ibimenyetso bimwe vyari kuri ayo masenge vyerekana ko yavuye mu yafashwe akugaranwa kandi agashirwako amagufuri na reta y’Uburundi
 Urudandazwa rw’amasenge y’inzovu rwaciwe mu Burundi mu 1987
 Mu 2004, abahinga mu bijanye n’urudandazwa rw’inyamaswa, Traffic International, bihweje ubwo bubiko bwarimwo hafi toni 84, zari  zigizwe n’amasenge 15
000
 Amagufuri ya douane yaciye ashirwa kuri izo konteneri indwi zarimwo ayo masenge
 Ariko kuva mu 2015, mu vyagiye birafatwa irya n’ino kw’isi, hari ibimenyetso vyerekanye ko inkomoko ari Uburundi
 BBC yarondeye ubushikiranganji bw’Uburundi  bujejwe ibidukikije ariko nta nyishu yaronse ku bibazo vyacu ku bijanye n’ubwo bubiko
 Kuri abo bahinga, gushika ubu vuba  reta yemeza ko aho ayo masenge abitse hatigeze hakomwakomwa
 Umwigisha Prof Samuel Wasser wo kuri kaminuza ya  Washington akaba n’umuhinga mu vyigwa vy’ibinyabuzima n’unwandistsi w’iki cigwa ca vuba, avuga ko “izo konteneri zikwiye gusubira kwugururwa kugira ayo masenge arimwo asubire gupimwa”
 “Kubera reta ivuga ko ibiro vy’izo konteneri bitagabanutse, none vyoba bivuga ko bagurisha mu kinyegero amwe muri ayo masenge hanyuma bakaronka ayandi bagasubiriza aya kera?” “Niba biri uko, bizoba ari bibi cane”, nk’uko yabibwiye BBC News
 Ayo matohoza mashasha  yerekana ashimitse ko ibihugu vyinshi vya Afrika bibandanya kubika amesenge vyafashe kuva igihe urudandazwa rwayo rwabuzwa mu mategeko
 Bamwe mu bahinga baribaza igituma bihitamwo kuyashira mu bubiko aho kuyasambura, mu gihe amategeko mpuzamakungu asanzwe abuza kugurisha amasenge y’inzovu  avuye mu ruhigi rutemewe n’amategeko
 Ibiri mu bubiko kandi biba bifise ivyago vyo gushobora kwibwa nk’uko vyagenze muri Mozambique mu 2016
 Abashakashatsi babonye kandi ibimenyetso ko hari amasenge yafashwe hanyuma akagaruka mu rudandazwa rutemewe n’amategeko  biciye mu nzira ziteye amakenga
 Ariko hari abandi bavuga ko ivyafashwe bishobora kubikwa ku mvo z’ubushakashatsi,  kwigisha canke kumenya inkomoko
 Ishirahamwe ryitwa  Elephant Protection Initiative(EPI) ririko rirafasha ibihugu 15 vyo muri Afrika kubika neza  amasenge vyafashe ariko riranafasha bimwe kuyasambura
 John Scanlon wo muri EPI avuga ati: “ Amasenge y’inzovu nta gaciro k’urudandazwa afise, kandi ivyo bisa n’ibitazohinduka
 “Igihugu kimwe kimwe cose nico kimenya uko kivyifatamwo
 “Gishimye kuyabika, ni ukuyabika  ahatekanye kandi bikandikwa
 Asambuwe naho,  hakandikwa ivyasambuwe, n’ibipimo bigafatwa vy’aho amasenge yavuye”

Dikembe Mutombo yatwaye agashimwe ka All-Star muri NBA incuro umunani ariko aravurwa ikivyimba co mu bwonko
 Uwo mukinyi  w’imyaka 56 yavukiye muri Repuburika ye Demolrasi ya Congo (RDC) yamaze imyaka 18 akina mw'ihiganwa rya basketball rya NBA, mu migwi ya Denver Nuggets, Atlanta Hawks na Houston Rockets
