N﻿a Elsa Maishman BBC News Reta ya Uganda yatangaje ingingo zo kwugara uturere tubiri tubangamiwe n’ikiza karanda ca Ebola, mu gihe ico gihugu kiriko gikora uko gishoboye kugira gituze iki kiza
 Ububare, amazu y’ubutambiro y’ijoro, ibibanza vyo gusengeramwo be n’ivyo kwinezereza vyugawe i Mubende na Kassanda bihana urubibe, kandi hashizweho n’amategeko yo kutava muhira(couvre-feu/curfew)
 Iyi ngingo ni ukwisubirako ku mukuru w’igihugu ca Uganda yari aherutse kuvuga ko ingingo nk’izi zidakenewe
 Iki giza kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw’abantu 19 muri 58 bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye
 Gusa, igitigiri nyezina c’abanduye n’abamaze gupfa gishobora kuba kirenga aho
 Iki kiza catanguye mu ntango z’ukw’icenda i Mubende akarere kari ku birometero vyababa 80 uvuye ku mugwa mukuru Kampala, kandi kabandanya ari ikiririmbiro ryaco
 Imbere y’aha, Perezida Museveni yari yiyamirije ivyo gutaramura, avuga ko Ebola atari umugera uca mu muyaga, ko rero idasaba ingingo nk’iza Covid-19
 Ariko nijoro ku wa gatandatu yahagaritse uruja n’uruza rwose mu turere twa Mubende na Kassanda mu kiringo c’imisi 21
 Avuga ariko ko amakamyo atwara ibintu azobandanya yinjira asohoka muri utwo turere, ariko ko ibindi bikorwa vyose vyo kwunguruza abantu bizotegerezwa guhagarara
 Muri iryo jambo yacishije ku mboneshakure, yavuze ati: "Izi ni ingingo z’igihe gito kugira ngo duhagarike ikwirakwira rya Ebola
 "Dutegerezwa gukorana n’abategetsi kugira ngo duhagarike iki kiza mu gihe gito gishoboka”
 Perezida Museveni yari yamaze gutegeka igipolisi guhagarika umuntu uwo ari we wese yiketsweko uwu mugera ariko akanka kwitaramura
 Yabujije kandi na ba rumenyi/abapfumu kudahirahira ngo barondere kuvura abanduye uwu mugera
 Mu biza vy’imbere y’aha, ba rumenyi bagiye bagirizwa ko bari mu batuma umugera ukwirakwira
 Umuntu wa mbere yishwe n’iki kiza ni umugabo w’imyaka 24 w’i Mubende
 Abantu batandatu bo mu muryango wiwe nabo nyene barapfuye
 Cahavuye gishika no ku mugwa mukuru Kampala, aho umwe aherutse gupfa muri kuno kw’icumi
 Ariko abajejwe amagara y’abantu bavuga ko ata mugera uranwa muri iki gisagara, kuko uyo mugabo yapfuye yari avuye i Mubende
 Iki kiza c’ubu giterwa n’umugera wamuka muri Sudani, uwu nawo ukaba ata rucanco rwawo ruraboneka
 Umugera uzwi “nk’umugera wa Zaire” - umugera wahitanye abantu 11
000 mu kiza karanda cadutse muri Afrika y’Uburengero kuva 2013 gushika 2016 - wowo urucanco rwawo ruriho
 Ebola yandukira iyo umuntu akorakoye amazimazi y’umubiri w’uwanduye canke ikintu canduye
 Mu bimenyetso vyayo harimwo kudahwa, gucibwamwo, rimwe na rimwe kandi no kuvira amaraso imbere canke hanze
 Igihe co kwibonekeza gishobora kuva ku misi ibiri gushika ku ndwi zitatu, kandi uwu mugera ushobora kugiriranira isano n’izindi ndwara nka malaria na typhoid

Amakungu abandanya atera akamo ko intambara yo mu ntara ya Tigray igoswe n’ingabo za Ethiopia ihagarara
 Ni mu gihe kuva mu misi mike iheze ibintu vyasubiye kwunyuka mu turere twinshi, harimwo Shire, igisagara gihaye indaro ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’abataye izabo
 Ingabo za Tigray ziherutse kwagiriza igisirikare ca Ethiopia hamwe n’incuti zaco za Eritrea ko babandanya bacucagira amabombe hagati no hanze y’iki gisagara
 Ishirahamwe ry’abatabazi International Rescue Committee rivuga ko umukozi waryo yari umwe mu basivire baherutse kwicigwa muri ico gisagara
 Inyuma y’aho hasubiriye kwaduka indyane zigatuma utwigoro tw’ubutabazi muri iyo ntara dukwama kuva mu kwa munani, amashirahamwe y’ubutabazi aratera akamo atabaza ko izi ndyane zishobora gutuma ibintu biyangara kandi vyari bisanzwe ari bibi
 i﻿biganiro vyari bitegekanijwe mu ndwi iheze mu ntumbero yo gutorera umuti izi ndyane zirangwa muri ino ntara yo mu buraruko bwa Ethiopia vyarungurijwe ku mvo z'uburyo
 Umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU, Antonio Guterres, avuga ko atewe impungenge n’ingene ingwano zasubiye kuba ndanse, agasaba ashimitse ko zihagarara
 Josep Borrell Fontelles ajejwe imigenderanire mw’ishirahamwe ry’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya nawe avuga ko ababajwe cane n’indyane hamwe n’abasivire baterwa muri ico gisagara ca Shire
 Addis Ababa ntaco iravuga ko aya majambo ariko imbere y’aha yahakanye ko idatera abasivire
 Ku ruhande rwayo,  mw’itangazo yasohoye ku wa gatandatu, Eritrea yavuze ko ivyo yagirizwa n’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya ko “ifise uruhara rwo gusambura” mu ntambara ya Tigray ko ari “ugutoteza n’ibigirankana abahitanwa n’iyi ntambara yahiswemwo na TPLF”
 Umukuru w’ishirahamwe USAID  Samantha Power yanditse ku rubuga rwa Twitter uno musi ku wa Mungu avuga ko “ibitero vy’urudavagi” bikorwa n’ingabo za Ethiopia n’iza Eritrea, ndetse n’uko bishoboka ko iz’iki gihugu ca Eritrea “zishobora vuba kwigarurira ibigo vy’abasivire, biteye impungengen nyinshi”
 Umunyamabanga wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire Anthony Blinken yateye akamo ingabo za Ethiopia n’iza Eritrea guhagarika “ibitero rusangi” vyavyo, ingabo za Tigray nazo “guhagarika ibikorwa vy’agasomborotso”
 Ntibiboneka neza nimba Addis Ababa n’ingabo za Tigray bazosubira ku meza y’ibiganiro inyuma y’aho ibiganiro vy’intangamarara vyari bitegekanijwe gutangura mu ndwi iheze vyugururijwe ku mvo zivugwa ko ari iz’uburyo
 Ariko umushikiranganji wa Ethiopia ajejwe ikigega ca reta, Eyob Tekalign, aho ari muri kino gihe i Washington mu nama y’ikigega mpuzamakungu n’ibanki y’isi yose, avuga ko yizeye ko hazoba ibiganiro vy’amahoro mu “ndwi nkeya ziri imbere”

Mu misi mike iheze, twarumvise ikirwanisho co gukingira ikirere kizwi nka IRIS-T, inkinzo rutura yo gukorora ibisasu vya misire,  cahawe Ukraine gitanzwe n’Ubudagi muri ino ndwi
 Iki kirwanisho gitanzwe inyuma y’aho Ukraine isabiye incuti zayo kuyiha izindi mfashanyo inyuma y’ibibombe Uburusiya bwacucagiye ku bisagara bitari bike, harimwo mbere n’umugwa mukuru Kyiv, mu ntango z’iyi ndwi
 Inyuma y’umubonano ku cicaro cavyo i Buruseri (Bruxelles/Brussels) mu Bubirigi, ibihugu 50 bicuditse na Ukraine mw’ishirahamwe ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe OTAN/NATO vyatangaje ko bigiye kurungikira iki gihugu gihanganye n’Uburusiya ibirwanisho rutura vyo gukingira ikirere
 Mu birwanisho vyemewe n’ibihugu nk’Ubwongereza, Canada, Ubufaransa n’Ubuholande, harimwo za misire n’ama radars
 Imbere y’aha, Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zari zayemereye nk’ibi nyene
 Ariko ata gushidikanya, iki kirwanisho c’ubuhinga buhanitse catanzwe n’Ubudagi ni co kivugwa cane gusumba kubera ari kimwe mu bigezweho gusumba kw’isi
 Mu kwerekana umunezero wiwe, umushikiranganji  wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi, Oleksii Reznikov, yanditse kuri Twitter ati: "Igihe gishasha mu gisata co kwivuna umwansi catanguye muri Ukraine
 Ibirwanisho vya IRIS-T vy’Ubudagi vyamaze gushika hano”
 Ubudagi bwiyemeje kurungika bine muri bino birwanisho rutura vyo gucungera ikirere, n’aho Kyiv bizoba ngombwa ko irindira gushika mu mwaka uza kugira ngo bitatu bindi bisigaye birungikwe
 Nk’uko reta y’Ubudagi ibivuga, iki kirwanisho nico ca mbere ca none mu buhinga bwo gukingira ikirere mu Budagi
 Ibirwanisho vyo gukingira ikirere bikoreshwa mu kuzibira ibitero vyo mu kirere ku banyagihugu, ku nyubakwa nyamukuru, ku bikoresho no ku ngabo zirwanira ku butaka
 Cane cane, iki kirwanisho IRIS-T kirasa ku ntera yo hagati ariko hejuru cane mu kirere, kigenewe gukingira igisagara gito
 Gishobora gukorora indege, ibisasu vya misire be na za ndege zitagira abadereva, zizwi nka drones
 IRIS-T SL, ikirwanisho gishasha co muri ubu bwoko, cageragejwe neza ku ncuro ya mbere mu 2014 imbere y’abaserukira amakungu
 Diehl Defense, ikigo c’Ubudagi cahinguye ubwoko bw’iki kirwanisho, ivuga ko ubu buhinga “bushobora kubandanya bukingira akarere mu gihe kirekire”
 Diehl yongerako iti: "Ikoresheje ubuhinga butandukanye bwa ‘radar’ na ‘commande’, IRIS-T itanga ubushobozi bwo hejuru cane mu gukingira ikirere”
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’ikinyamakuru co mu Budagi Der Spiegel, ubu buhinga “bugizwe n’imodoka zitatu: ikamyo ya gisirikare itwara inkoho ishobora kurasa misile umunani, imodoka ya radar, n'imodoka ya commande"
 Der Spiegel  congerako kiti: "Misire zikorora indege zishobora kugema ikiri ku ntera y’ibirometero 40 hamwe na 20 uja hejuru”
 Ku ruhande rwayo, iradiyo y’Abadagi Deutsche Welle ivuga ko ibisasu vya misire vya IRIS -T bikoresha amasanamu y’imishwarara (images infrarouges/ infrared images) mu kubona neza aho bishaka kugema kandi ko bishobora guterwa kuri degree 360 uvuye aho biterewe
 Igisata ca BBC gikoresha ururimi rw’ikirusiya kivuga kandi ko radar y’ubu buryo  ikomeye cane, ibi bikayituma ishobora kubona bitagoranye igisasu ca misire kigendera hafi
  Hampande y’ibi, ifise ububasha bwo guhiga no gusambura indege, ibisasu canke za drone nyinshi ica rimwe
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine amaze amezi atari make asaba incuti ziwe ubuhinga bwo gukingira ikirere bushobora kuba “nk’inkinzo yo mu kirere” ya Ukraine
 Igisirikare ca Ukraine kivuga ko IRIS-T ishobora gukingira igihugu “iterabwoba”
 Avugana na Deutsche Welle, umuhinga mu vyo kwivuna abansi mu gisata kijejwe imigenderanire mw’ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Bulaya, Rafael Loss, avuga ko ubu buhinga bushasha “buzokomeza cane igisata ca Ukraine kijejwe kwivuna abansi mu gihe buzoba burungitswe”
 Icakora, aragabisha ko ubu atizeye ko ari “impinduka nyazo zitangazwa n’abanya-Ukraine bamwe bamwe”, n’aho bitanga amahirwe ko ubu “ibibanza vya gisivire na gisirikare bike ari vyo bizoshikirwa n’ibitero”
 Zelensky we nyene ubwiwe, ku wa kane, itariki 13 Gitugutu (10), yavuze ko Ukraine ubu ifise “10% y’ivyo ikeneye” mu rwego rwo gukingira ikirere
 Ukraine iracafise za misire zo gukorora indege zakora muri ca gihe c’ubutegetsi bw’Abasoviyeti, ubu ikaba iriko irarondera kuzishira ku rugero rwa none ku buryo ihabwa n’incuti zayo
 Hagati aho, igisirikare ca Ukraine carashoboye guhangana n’ic’Uburusiya muri ano mezi umunani aheze kuva intambra itanguye
 Kivuga kiti: "Nk’akarorero, muri vya bitero bikomeye vyo ku wa 10-11 Gitugutu, ingabo za Ukraine zirwanira mu kirere zarashoboye gukorora 60% za misire z’Uburusiya”
 Nta nkeka ko IRIS-T y’Ubudagi hamwe n’ibindi birwanisho vyemewe n’ibihugu vya OTAN bizotsimbataza ubushobozi bwa Ukraine bwo guhangana n’ibitero vy’Uburusiya, ariko nk’uko abahinga be na Zelensky we nyene ubwiwe babivuga, Ukraine izobandanya ikenera ibindi birwanisho bitangwa n’incuti zayo

A﻿batwa bo muri Uganda ni abantu babayeho nk'abahigi mu mashamba yabo mu gihe c'ibinjana vyinshi cane
 A﻿riko mu myaka ya 90, barirukanywe na reta mu ntumbero yo gukingira inguge ziba mu mashamba amwe na bo
 E﻿ric Tumuhairwe, ari mw'ishirahamwe ry'abatwa muri Uganda agira ati: "Nshaka gusubira mu buzima twahora tubamwo
" Ivyegeranyo bitangwa n'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU abantu bababa imiriyaridi 1
6 - harimwo n'abasangwabutaka bababa imiliyoni 70 - bifashisha amashamba kugira babeho
 U﻿murwi w'abahinga kw'ihindagurika ry'ibihe uvuga ko ihonywa ry'amashamba bituma ibice 17% vy'ivyuka vy'ubumara vyisuka mu kirere
 U﻿kwirukanwa kw'abo batwa mu ntumbero yo gukingira ibikoko n'ibidukikije, nk'uko bivugwa n'umushakashatsi Guillaume Blanc, ni ingaruka ry'iragi ry'abakoroni
 Ubukoloni bw'icatsi kibisi
 U﻿mushakashatsi w'umufaransa Guillaume Blanc, yanditse igitabo "The invention of green colonialism"
 Mu ntumbero yo  kurangiza iciswe "Eden nyafrika", avuga ko ubukoloni bw'icatsi kibisi bwavuye mu ciyumviro co kuva ku bukoloni
 K﻿uri we ni nk'indoto ya "Afrika y'icatsi kibisi, y'isugi, ishamba cimeza ariko ribamwo abantu benshi, ryononwa cane rikwiye gukingirwa n'abanye Afrika"
 I﻿bi rero bisigura iyirukanwa ry'abantu bose mu mashamba ashobora kuzohinduka imbuga kama nk'uko abandanya abivuga
 U﻿wo mushakashatsi agira ati: "Inyuma y'ubukoloni, ico gikorwa carabandanije
 intumbero yarahindutse ariko agatima karacahari"
 U﻿bu, nk'uko abivuga, ico ciyumviro cerekana "igikorwa c'amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu  nka UNESCO, WWF ashaka kwigarurira Afrika ku nguvu
" A﻿sigura ati: "Hakugerageza gutatura amatati ajanye n'ibidukikije nk'uko bikorwa  i Buraya mu gufasha abarimyi  n'aborozi bene ubutaka muri Afrika, ayo mashirahamwe agerageza kubakurako ubumuntu
" B﻿lanc avuga ati: "Abarimyi n'aborozi ibihumbi n'ibihumbi barirukanwa  mu mashamba, abandi nkabo bagacibwa ihadabu  bakanapfungwa kubera barimye agataka canke baharagiye ibitungwa vyabo"
 M﻿u 2019, ikigega mpuzamakungu kijejwe ibidukikije (WWF) baragirijwe gutanga amahera no gukorana n'abagwanya abahigi b'ibikoko boba barishe rubozo baranica abantu mu mbuga kama muri Aziya no muri Afrika, nk'uko biri mu matohoza yagizwe na Buzzfeed
 I﻿shirahamwe mpuzamakungu rijejwe gucungera amashamba ryariyemeje "gukora neza" inyuma y'ivyo vyagiriji vyo kutubahiriza agateka ka zina muntu
 A﻿riko, nk'uko bivugwa na Guillaume Blanc, ibihugu vya Afrika vyasigaranye impongore kama zashizweho mu gihe c'ubukoloni vyarabandanije gukora gutyo
 B﻿asigaranye iryo ragi, nk'uko bivugwa n'uwo mwanditsi, kubera imvo z'ubutunzi kubera impongore kama ziza kurabwa n'abantu benshi, kuri vyo rero ni ku mpamvu y'amahera
 B﻿lanc kandi avuga ko izo mpongore zituma "amareta ashira amabendera mu turere bitayorohera kugenzura"
 C﻿o kimwe n'abatwa, abasangwabutaka b'i Buziralo mu karere ka Kalehe mu gihugu ca Republika ya Demokrasi ya Congo bahora baba mu ruhongore kama rwa Kahuzi-Biega (PNKB), na bo nyene nyene barirukanywe ku butaka bwabo"
 Philippe Libaku Kafundo yabwiye BBC ati: "D﻿ushaka gusubira mu mashamba kuko ni bwo butaka bwacu
 Ubu nta matongo tukigira, abantu bacu bamerewe nabi cane"
 M﻿u 2018, aba Mbilikimo barashatse kugaruka muri PNKB
 A﻿riko ntivyagenze neza
 Mu gihe rimwe na rimwe bagiriza kugira uruhigi rudakurikije amategeko, kenshi na kenshi baratana mu mitwe n'abajejwe gucungera amashamba muri PNKB
 K﻿afundo agira ati: "Abantu bacu batatu barafashwe barapfungwa bahuye n'abajejwe umutekano mw'ishamba bariko barakizura"
 A﻿bandanya agira ati: "Bafashwe nk'abagizi ba nabi bonona uruhongore kama rwa Kahuzi-Biega mu gihe bariko baraja aho bavukiye muri iryo shamba"
 B﻿avugana na BBC, abarongoye uruhongore kama rwa Kahuzi-Biega batubwiye ko twokoresha inkuru yanditse ku rubuga rwabo rwa internet
 K﻿u rubuga rwa PNKB handitse ko mu kwezi kwa kabiri mu 2022, abajejwe gucungera amashamba mu gihugu (WCS) mu ruhongore rwa Kahuzi-Biega barerekanye uburyo bushasha butumbereye "guheba akarenganyo kahora gakorerwa abasangwabutaka, bafatwe neza kugira kabe akarorero mu kubungabungwa, hisunzwe agateka ka zina muntu
 Kuri urwo rubuga handitse hati: "A﻿masezerano yo gufashanya hagati y'ibisata vya reta n'ivyo abikorera utwabo yarateweko igikumu  kugira ashire imbere " gutanguza uburyo bwo gusangira ku mugaragaro atawurushije uwundi inyungu, gushiraho uburyo bwo kugenzura ubutunzi kama  bijanye n'imico n'imigenzo, guhanahana ivyiyumviro ku mico n'uburenganzira bw'abakoresha ishamba, hamwe n'uburyo bwo gusubiza hamwe hagati y'abatwa na reta mu kuvugana ibibabakiye no kurenganywa bagiye bakorerwa"
 F﻿ranklin Bombwe ashinzwe igisata c'amategeko mu kigo kijejwe gufasha aba Mbilikimo n'abari mu ngorane zikome (CAMV)
 Agira ati: "Ni ngombwa dutandukanye guhiga ahatarekuriwe n'amategeko n'uruhigi rw'abasangwabutaka, bisigura ko bakenera ibikoko bito bito kugira babeho, ivyo bikaba bidasigura ko kwonoza ibiterwa kugira barye
" Hakubangamira ibidukikije, nk'uko abandanya abivuga, imico n'akaranga vy'abasangwabutaka birahimiriza kubibungabunga
 Kubwa Kafundo n'umuryango wiwe, kuronswa ubutaka bwa basokuru babo n'ikintu gikomeye  cane kuri bo
 Hanze y'amashamba, ubuzima bwabo bwarabangamiwe cane
 Yidoga agira ati: "H﻿ari kandi n'imiti twebwe abatwa turondera mw'ishamba, tutari mw'ishamba rero, ntidushobora kuyironka no kuyibungabunga
 "Ni mw'ishamba kandi abatwa bashobora kwerekana imico n'imigenzo vyabo"
 A﻿mashirahamwe nk'irya Francklin Bombwe, CAMV, aragabisha ku buzima bw'abasangwabutaka birukanywe ku butaka bwabo
 Bombwe avuga ati: "Ubu baba mu bigwati bibakira kandi nta kintu na kimwe bafise
 Nta mfungurwa, nta butaka kandi ntibazi no kurima
" A﻿batwa bahora batunzwe no guhiga hamwe no kwamura ivyamwa/imbuto mw'ishamba ubu biba ngombwa ko barondera ubuzi kugira bashobore kubaho
