" K﻿ugira bafungure, rimwe na rimwe bakorera abandi ku musi ku musi
 Kubwa Franklin Bombwe, kuba batize bisigura ko "agashahara kabo ari gato, urumva rero ko badashobora kuronka ivyo bipfuza vyose"
