Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya avuga ko ata bindi bitero bikomeye bikenewe muri Ukraine, imisi mike inyuma y’ibibombe bikomeye bitari bike vyatewe kuri iki gihugu kuva intambara itangura
 Avuga ko ibibanza hafi  vyose vyari vyateguwe guterwa vyarashwe, kandi ko intumbero yiwe itari ugusambura Ukraine
 Avuga kandi ko intumbero ya Moscou yo kwinjiza abantu 300
000 mu gisirikare izoba yashitsweko mu ndwi zibiri
 Avuze ibi mu gihe ingabo z’Uburusiya ahenshi ziriko zisubira inyuma, Ukraine nayo igenda itera intambwe, inyuma y’amezi amezi hafi umunani kuva iyi ntambara itanguye
 Avugana n’abanyamakuru inyuma y’ikoraniro ryahuje abategetsi b’akarere ku mugwa mukuru  wa Kazakhstan, Astana, umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yavuze ko ibibanza 22 kuri 29 vyari vyateguwe guterwa muri Ukraine vyarashwe kandi ko igisirikare “kiriko kirashikira indwi bindi bisigaye”
 Ati: "Nta bitero bikomeye bigikenewe
 Ubu dufise ibindi bikorwa”
 Kuva ku wa mbere, Uburusiya bwatanguje igihuhusi c’ibitero vya misire ku bisagara bitari bike vya Ukraine, mu co Putin avuga ko kwari ukwihora igitero cakozwe ku kiraro gikomeye gifatanya Uburusiya n’akarere ka Crimée/Crimea bwigaruriye
 Abantu batari bake barasize ubuzima muri ibi bitero abandi barakomereka, inyubakwa nazo zirononekara
 Uturere two hagati tw’umugwa mukuru Kyiv natwo nyene twarashikiriwe ku ncuro ya mbere kuva intambara yaduka
 Ariko Putin avuga ko intumbero y’Uburusiya itari gusambura Ukraine, ariko ntiyicuza kuri iki gitero
 Ati: "Muri make ibiriko biraba ntibiryoshe
 Ariko aho nyene, [n’iyo Uburusiya budatera], ibintu biba bimeze uko bimeze, ariko gusa ibintu biba ari bibi cane kuri twebwe
 Rero turiko dukora ibintu vyose neza kandi mu gihe nyaco”
 Perezida Putin avuga ko abantu 200
000 bamaze kwinjizwa mu gisirikare, kandi ko muri bo 16
000 bamaze gushika ku rugamba
 Yongerako y’uko abona ko bidakenewe ko abandanya atera akamo ngo abantu biyandikishe
 Hagati aho, akamo yateye kateje uburakari burenze urugero mu Burusiya, bituma abagabo ibihumbi n’ibihumbi bahungira mu bihugu bibanyi
 BBC kandi yabonye ko abaherutse kwinjizwa ata nyigisho zikwiye bahawe imbere y’uko barungikwa ku rugamba
 Ni mu gihe igisata ca BBC gikoresha ururimi rw’ikirusiya kivuga ko camenye abasirikare b’Uburusiya barenga 7500 bamaze gupfira mu ntambara ya Ukraine
 Igitigiri c’abamaze kuhapfira kizwi ko ari kinini cane, mbere hari n’amakuru avuga ko bamwe mu baherutse kwinjizwa  bishwe
 Avuga ku migenderanire n’ivyahoze bigize Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti, Perezida Putin ashimangira ko ata ngorane intambara yateye kuri vyo
 Avuga ko ari ibisanzwe ko ibihugu bimwe bimwe bigira impungenge ariko ko abandanya abibwira uko ibintu bimeze igihe cose
 Hagati aho, abihweza ibintu n’ibindi bavuga ko ikibanza Uburusiya bufise mu karere kiriko kiragabanuka, mu gihe abakuru b’ibihugu nka Kassym-Jomart wa Kazakhstan  bariko bitandukanya na Putin kuri ino ntambara

N﻿a Jonathan Beale BBC News, Bakhmut Inyuma y’amezi hafi umunani kuva igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine gitanguye, ingabo zabwo ntizorohewe mu gihe Ukraine iriko itera intambwe yigarurira ubutaka mu buseruko no mu bumanuko
 Mu karere ka Donbas kari mu buseruko, ingabo z’Uburusiya ziracarondera kwigarurira igisagara ca Bakhmut kandi ziriko ziratera intambwe
 Iki gisagara cumvikanamwo vya muzinga vy’urutavanako, ijoro n’umurango
 Amayinga atari make araheze ari uku
 Abanyagihugu ba Bakhmut bangana na 70
000 hafi bose baramaze guhunga
 Abasigayeyo nka bose ni abatama
 Nta mazi, nta matara
 Umurongo muto w’abantu bakirondera guhungishwa niwo uboneka, imodoka ntoya y’abagiraneza niyo igenda igaruka muri ico gisagara
 Olena w’imyaka 70 yari umwe muri abo bari barindiriye guhungishwa
 Uyu mutamakazi ati: "Abantu bararushe”, aho nyene ibindi bisasu vya muzinga vyariko birasirana muri ico gisagara
 Buri muntu aca yifata uko bimujemwo, nk’uko abivuga – bamwe bakanywa itabi, abandi bakarondera ico guhekenya, mu gihe abandi nabo bicara aho bakuzura amarira
 Ubuzima bwaranse, nk’uko abivuga, kuko bateka hanze, bakamana indobo ku mutwe baja kuvoma amazi
 Ati: "Ndavumye uyu muntu yatanguje iyi ntambara
 Ndamuvumye incuro 100”
 Igihe yari yuriye imodoka yagaranzuye amaboko mu kwishimira ko yari ashoboye kuva muri ako kaga
 I Bakhmut, Uburusiya buriko bwita m uziko bugerageza guhindura ibivugwa kuri ino ntambara
 Ni kimwe mu bibanza bike ingabo zitariko zirasubira inyuma
 Intambwe ziterwa hano zigenda buke buke kandi zikiha inkumbi, ariko ingabo z’Uburusiya zigenda zigarurira ubutaka
 Kumbure hari impamvu Uburusiya bwashize inguvu zidasanzwe kuri Bakhmut
 Mu ntango za rino ci, bwari bwigaruriye  ibisagara vya Severodonetsk na Lysychansk
 Bakhmut yategerezwa gukurikira, vyari vyitezwe ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zari guca rero zisatira Kramatorsk na Sloviansk
 Ariko aha hari igihe Ukraine itari bwatangure ibitero giturumbuka vyo kwivuna mu buseruko no mu bumanuko
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya zarirukanywe amaja mu buraruko
 Ibisagara vya Kramatorsk na Sloviansk ntibigishobora gushikirwa na vya muzinga vy’Uburusiya nk’uko vyari bimeze mu kw’indwi
 Uburusiya ku ruhande runini vyabaye ngombwa ko buhindura amayeri, bukarwana intambara yo kwivuna, hakurwana intambara yo gutera
 Koroneri (Col) Serhiy Cherevatyi, umuvugizi w’ingabo za Ukraine zirwanira mu buseruko, aracafise amakenga ko Abarusiya boba bagisigaranye abantu bakwiye n’uburyo bwo kwigarurira Bakhmut – ari naho bwashize inguvu nyinshi cane za gisirikare ubu, nk’uko abivuga
 Aho nyene, nk’uko abivuga, Uburusiya buriko buragerageza kwubaka ibirindiro vyo kwivuna hirya mu buraruko mu micungararo y’ibisagara vya Svatove and Kremenna – naho nyene amayira nyamukuru yo gushikana uburyo ku rugamba akaba ageramiwe n’ingabo za Ukraine
 Col Cherevatyi avuga ko ubu vyinshi bizovana n’igitigiri c’ingabo nshasha Uburusiya bushobora kwegeranya hamwe n’ubushobozi bwazo
 “Gushika ubu, turabona ko bagoyagoya kandi ntabirwanisho bikwiye bafise”
 Nasanze uyu mukoroneri mu bisigarira vy’ikimodoka ntamenwa c’Uburusiya casambuwe be n’imodoka z’intambara hafi y’igisagara ca Lyman giherutse kwigarurirwa
 Niyo sanamu y’igisirikare c’Uburusiya Ukraine ishaka kwereka amakungu – iracabuza abanyamakuru gushika ahabera intambara
 Col Cherevatyi avuga ko Uburusiya buherutse kurungika ku rugamba ibimodoka ntamenwa vya kera bizwi nka T62, vyakozwe mu myaka ya 1960, kubera vyinshi mu bikoresho bigezweho vyasambuwe
 Mu kwezi guheze, Perezida Putin yatangaje ko ategerezwa kwinjiza mu gisirikare abantu 300
000 kugira baje kurwana, Uburusiya ubu bukavuga ko buzoba bwabakwijije mu ndwi zibiri uhereye ubu
 Ariko utwigoro two kwigarurira Bahkmut turiko dukorwa n’abarwanyi b’umurwi Wagner, nk’uko igenedera rya gisirikare ry’Ubwongereza ribibona
 Uyu murwi w’abacangero urwanira muri Ukraine kuva mu 2014, mu kwezi guheze hakaba hari videwo yasohotse yerekana umukuru wawo ariko arondera abarwanyi mw’ibohero ryo mu Burusiya
 Yabwiye Abarusiya ati: "Ni ibigo vya gisirikare vyigenga n’abapfungwa, canke abana banyu – ifatire ingingo wewe nyene”
 Biracashoboka ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zishobora kwigarurira Bakhmut
 Ariko none haca hakurikira iki? Col Cherevatyi  ati: "Igihe tuva muri Lysychansk twararuhishije umwansi”
 Yiteze ko bishobora kugenda uko nyene muri Bakhmut
  Nayo ku vyerekye iyongerekana ry’ibitero vya misire vy’Uburusiya biraswa kure, avuga ko ikintu conyene bizokora ni ukwongerereza intege Ukraine: "Turabakubita ku rugamba, ikintu conyene basigaranye ni ibisasu vya misire”

Intwazangabo ya gisirikare irongoye ingabo ziherutse gutembagaza ubutegetsi muri Burkina Faso yagenywe kuba umukuru w’igihugu gushika mu kw’indwi 2024
 Inama nkuru y’igihugu yaraye itangaje ko Kapiteni (Capt) Ibrahim Traoré atazokwemererwa kwitoza mu matora ategekanijwe ico gihe
 Haciye indwi zibiri yatse ubutegetsi Liyetena-Jenerali (Lt-Gen) Paul-Henri Damiba, nawe nyene yari yashitse ku butegetsi mu kwa mbere atembagaje ubwahahora, akagiriza reta ico gihe ko yari yananiwe no kurwanya inyeshamba ziyitirira idini rya Islam
 Hagati aho, ibintu vyabandanije biyangara kuva uyu mu Jenerali afashe ubutegetsi, bituma na we  rero abogozwa na Capt Traoré ku nguvu
 Capt Traoré ni we ntwazangabo aherutse gushikira ubutegetsi vuba atembagaje ubwahahora mu rukurikirane rw’itembagazwa ry’ubutegetsi rurangwa mu bihugu vyahoze bitwarwa gikoloni n’Ubufaransa muri Afrika y’Uburengero
 Bivanye n’uko ata nzego za demokarasi zikomeye muri ico gihugu, aho ingabo zimaze igihe kinini ziganje, Capt Traoré yarafashe ubutegetsi yiyemeza kugarukana umutekano mu gihugu kirangwamwo ubwoba bw’inyeshamba
 Itembagazwa ry’ubutegetsi yakoze - irya kabiri muri Burkina Faso mu gihe kitarenga amezi icenda - ni co kimenyetso ca nyuma c’ikiza karanda c’ama coups d’Etat umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU António Guterres yashikirijeko impungenge mu 2021
 Ico gihe, Guterres yavuze ati: “Ico nsaba, neza neza - cane cane ibihugu vya rutura – ni uko bija hamwe ku neza y’ubumwe bw’Inama nkuru ijejwe umutekano kw’isi bigahagarika aka karanda k’ama coups d’Etat”
 Ariko rero kubera ibihugu bikomeye kw’isi birajwe ishinga n’ibibera mu bihugu vyabo  - canke kandi n’intambara yo muri Ukraine – ntivyitayeho cane umutekano muke urangwa mu bihugu nka za Burkina Faso

Teklemariam Bekit & Farouk Chothia B﻿BC News Abategetsi muri Eritrea bakomeje igikorwa co kwegeranya abitaba urugamba kandi barahiga uwo wese atitavye akamo mu gihugu cose, mu gihe intambara muri Ethiopia bihana urubibe yongeye gukomera, nk’uko amasoko menshi muri Ethiopia yabibwiye BBC
 Imikwabu y’ubu vuba niyo ya mbere mibi kuko n’abagore ntibahawe agahengwe, aho n’abavyeyi b’abagore n’abagabo bageze mu za bukuru bafatwa bagapfungwa kugirango  bahate abana babo, baba bagiye kwinyegeza bishikane, nk’uko bavuga
 Bavuze ariko bemerewe kudashira ahabona umwidondoro wabo kuko Eritrea irimwo ubwisanzure buke aho reta igenzura hafi buri kintu cose c’ubuzima bw’abanyagihugu
 Eritrea yarungitse ingabo gufasha ingabo za Ethiopia kurwanya iz’intara ya Tigray mu buraruko bw’ico gihugu, intara isanzwe ihana urubibe na Eritrea
 Isoko rimwe rivuga ko “kubera hari benshi batitavye akamo, imikwabu yakomejwe” ryongerako ko abagore bafashwe bagapfungwa  kubera abagabo babo bagerageje kutitaba ibikorwa vya gisirikare
 Bariyeri zarashinzwe ku mabarabara makuru makuru , ikuzako ryo gusaka naryo rikaba ririko riraba mu bisagara n’ibigwati
 Ku mugwa mukuru, Asmara,  abantu bafatirwa mu mabarabara mu gihe mu gihugu hagati naho , abategetsi bagota  ingo, bakanyaga ibitungwa canke bagatera ubwoba abo mu muryango mu gihe umuntu aronderwa atabonetse, nk’uko BBC yabwiwe
 BBC yarondeye reta ya Eritrea kugira hagire ico ibivuzeko
 Mu kwezi guheze, umushikiranganji ajejwe amakuru Yemane Gebremeskel yavuze ko “igitigiri gito cane” c’ingabo z’integabizoza ari bo bahamagawe, ahakana ko  akamo karekeye abanyagihugu bose
 Iyo ntambara imaze hafi imyaka ibiri muri Tigray n’intara bihana urubibe hari abihweza ibintu n’ibindi bavuga ko ihitana abantu benshi kurusha intambara yo muri Ukraine
 Ariko ntigaragara mu binyamakuru cane nk’iyo muri Eritrea kuko reta za Eritrea na Ethiopia zibuza cane ingendo nayo imirongo ya gutumatumanako muri Tigray ikaba yaraciwe
 Umugambwe Tigrayan People’s Liberation Front (TPLF) ugenzura iyo ntara kandi ukaba ariwo urongoye iyo ntambara ugwana na reta mpuzamtara ya Ethiopia, nawo nyene ubu uri mw’isekeza ryo kurondera abaza kwongereza ingabo zawo
 Ivyo  bibaye aho agahengwe  kari karumvikanyweko kagwiriye mu mazi kamaze amezi atanu mu kwezi kw’umunani  naryo ishihamwe rya Afrika rikananirwa no gutanguza ibiganiro
 Isoko muri Eritrea rivuga ko abategetsi bagerageza “gukora abantu ku mitima” mu manama n’abanyagihugu, aho bafatanya ukwisuka muri iyo ntambara “n’ukubaho hamwe n’ubutavogerwa vy’igihugu”, kandi bakavuga ko TPLF “itegerezwa guhambwa”
 Mu kwezi guheze, Eritrea yahamagaje ingabo z’integabizoza  ku bafise munsi y’imyaka 55  hanyuma bamwe barungikwa ku rugamba
 Muri iyi minsi ya vuba, ingwano zaravuzwe  mu turere twinshi two ku mupaka, harimwo Adigrat, Rama, Shiraro na Zalambesa
 Ariko abanya-Eritrea benshi baranse kwitaba ako kamo, bavuga ko badashaka gupfira mu co babona  nk’intambara idakenewe
 Hari isoko ryavuze ko n’”abageze mu zabukuru nabo bahatiwe kwitaba urugamba mu turere twinship  kuko ahenshi, igikorwa co kujana abantu mu bikorwa vya gisirikare giba ata mategeko akurikijwe”
 Umunya-Eritrea aba  mu mahanga yashikirije  impungenge afitiye uwo bavukana hamwe na muramuwe ku murwa mukuru Asmara
 Yavuze ko umugore w’uwo bavukana yahunze n’abana babo aja mu kigwati iyo abavyeyi biwe baba, ariko avuga ko uwo bavukana yari agipfunzwe
 Abategetsi kandi ntibatanga udupapuro umuntu yerekana kugira ashobore kugura  ivyankenerwa nk’isukari n’amavuta ku giciro gito – gushika imiryango yitavye akamo, nk’uko amasoko abandanya abivuga
 Isoko ryabwiye BBC riti “ivyo bahora bakora mu gihugu hagati ubu nivyo bariko baragira ku murwa mukuru, banka guha imiryango utwo dupapuro, impusha n’ibindi”
 Abantu barazanwa ku biro vy’ubutegetsi bw’aho batumbereye, bakagabishwa ko “kunyegeza abana bawe canke umugabo, canke gufasha mu gutoroka bifatwa nk’uguhemukira igihugu”
 Iryo soko ryongeyeko ko  “batera umutima uhagaze abantu bikomeye cane”
 Umugore umwe muri Eritrea yavuze ko abantu benshi bababaye cane kuko intambara iguma imara abantu urunganwe ku rundi
 Uwo mugore abandanya ati: “Abantu berekana ko batabishigikiye mu buryo butandukanye, ariko abajejwe umutekano ni ba ruburakigongwe ku buryo bashobora gukorera abanyagihugu amahano ayariyo yose”
 Umunya-Eritrea aba hanze yavuze ko afitiye ubwoba uuryango wiwe uri mu gihugu
 Se wiwe w’imyaka 67 yari mu basirikare b’integabizoza yarungitswe ku rugamba mu karere kiwe, n’ubwo atari bwategekwe kuja ku rwasiro rw’intambara
 Ariko na cane cane yari afitiye ubwoba mushikiwe w’imyaka 23, avuga ko yari apfungiwe mw’ikambi ya gisirikare hafi y’igisagara ca Akurdet kiri mu burengero inyuma yo gufatwa ariko aragerageza kujabuka urubibe
 Uwo mugabo avuga ko “haheze igihe umuryango wiwe ata nkuru ziwe uronse, ubu nta wuzi irengero ryiwe
” Amasoko avuga ko abategetsi bakangisha gutwara abapfunzwe kure cane mu turere tugoye cane kubamwo
 Reta ifise  urufatangane rw’ibibanza vyo gupfungiramwo mu kinyegero aho abantu bapfungirwa bakamara imyaka ata mategeko ariko arakora, nk’uko imigwi iharanira agateka ka zina muntu avuga
 Intambara yadutse muri Tigray muri Munyonyo (11) mu 2020 hagati y’umushishikiranganji wa mbere akaba n’uwatsindiye agashimwe k’amahro ka Nobel Abi Ahmed na TPLF, bapfuye ibibazo bitandukanye, birimwo niba Ethiopia itegerezwa kugumana reta  mpuzantara ishingiye ku moko
 Iyo ntambara yadutse hasanzwe hari ukutarabana ryiza hagati ya reta ya Eritrea na TPLF, yamaze imyaka myinshi ariyo irongoye reta ya Ethiopia gushika Abiy Ahmed ashitse ku butegetsi mu 2018
 Ku ntwaro ya TPLF, Eritrea na Ethiopia vyaragwanye bipfa urubibe hapfa abantu bashika 80
000
 Sentare mpuzamakungu yahavuye ica urubanza ko Ethiopia isubiza ubutaka Eritrea, ariko reta irongowe na TPLF ivyo ntiyabikoze
 Eritrea yasubiye kuronka ubwo butaka aho iyi ntambara itanguriye mu kwezi kwa Munyonyo (11) mu 2020
 Mu myaka 28 imaze ironse intahe yo kwikukira kuri Ethiopia, Eritrea imaze kurwana intambara n’ababanyi bayo bose – Yemen mu 1995, Sudan mu 1996, Ethiopia kuva mu 1998 gushika mu 2000 na Djibouti mu 2008
 Itegeko ryo gukorera igihugu ivy’igisirikare ryategerezwa kumara amezi 18, ariko ryahavuye riba ntabanduka
 Mu myaka 20 iheze abanya-Eritrea bakiri bato baharurwa mu buhumbi n’ibihumbi barahunze igihugu kugira ntibaje muri ivyo bikorwa birimwo n’ibikorwa vyo ku gahato

Jenerali (Gen) Sergei Surovikin, azwi ku ritazirano nka Jenerali Armageddon, niyo ntwazangabo nshasha ya Perezida Vladimir Putin irongoye urugamba rwiwe muri Ukraine
 Igenwa ryiwe ryatangajwe amasaha makeya inyuma y’igitero ku kiraro ca Crimea/Crimée
 Umusi wiwe wa mbere mu bikorwa waranzwe n’igihuhusi c’ibisasu vya misire vy’Uburusiya – kimwe mu bitero bikomeye cane mu mezi atari make
 Ariko Gen Surovikin si mushasha muri ino ntambara iriko iradindira
 Yararongoye ingabo ku rugamba mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Ni mu gihe, hasigaye umusi umwe ngo intambara itangure, yari yafatiwe ibihano n’ibihugu vya Bulaya kubera ikibanza afise mu gisirikare hamwe n’imigenderanire afitaniye na Perezida Putin
 Ibi biboneka ko ari ubwa mbere Uburusiya bugenye ku mugaragaro intwazangabo irongora ibikorwa vyose vya gisirikare muri Ukraine – imbere y’aha, hari amakuru yavuga ko iki kibanza cari gifiswe na Jenerali Alexander Dvornikov
 Gen Surovikin yavutse mu 1966 avukira ahitwa Novosibirsk, akaba ari inzobere mu ntambara z’Uburusiya ziheruka
 Gen Surovikin yatanguriye ibikorwa vyiwe vya gisirikare muri Afghanistani mu mpera z’imyaka ya 1980
 Aha hari mu bihe “bitari vyoroshe na gato”, nk’uko bivugwa n’umwigisha wa kaminuza mu bijanye na kahise hamwe n’imico kama Peter Waldron – ico gihe Abasoviyeti bariko baratsindwa
 Prof Waldron avuga ko ibi vyamwubatse vyongera bituma uyu mu jenerali amenyekana cane kubera yagize uruhara mu “bikorwa vy’itoteza” kuva mu ntango
 Atahutse mu gihugu mu 1991, abantu batatu barishwe mu mishamirano hagati y’igisirikare n’abaharanira intwaro rusangi bari mu myiyerekano i Moscou
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’igisata ca BBC gikoresha ururimi rw’ikirusiya, abari mu myiyerekano ico gihe bazibiye inzira z’amamodokari ya gisirikare hanyuma Gen Surovikin, ari na we yari azirongoye, aca atanga itegeko ryo kubandanya urugendo
 Ibirego vyose vyarafuswe ku mvo z’uko yariko akora akurikije amategeko yahabwa
 Haciye imyaka ine, ico gihe akaba yari umunyeshure mw’ishure rya gisirikare ry’ahitwa Frunze, uyu mu jenerali yaciriwe igihano co gupfungwa ic’amaso yagiriwe n’icaha co kugurisha ibastola (pistolet) ku munyeshure bigana
 Yavuze ko wari “umugambi bari bateguye” mu nyuma iki gihano kikaba cahavuye gifutwa muri dosiye yiwe
 Uyu mu jenerali yarakoreye kandi no mu ndyane zo mu myaka ya 1990 muri Tajikistan na Chechnya/Tchétchénie, hamwe kandi no muri Syria ubu bwa vuba, igihe Moscou iza gufasha reta ya Perezida Bashar al-Assad w’iki gihugu mu 2015
 Nk’umukuru w’ishami rya gisirikare rirwanira mu kirere – n’aho atari amenyereye intambara zo mu kirere -  yarahagarikiye ifutwa ry’ikirere c’igisagara hafi cose ca Aleppo muri Syria
 Prof Waldron avuga ko ukwivanga kw’Uburusiya mu ndyane za Syria kwaranzwe n’ibibombe hamwe n’ibitero vy’urutavanako mu bibanza vy’abasivire
 Gen Surovikin niwe yari ahagarariye ivyo vyose kandi yari “yiteguye neza gukoresha ingingo zose zikenewe”
 Hagati aho, Charles Lister, umuyobozi w’igisata ca Syria kijejwe imigambi ku kigo Middle East Institute, avuga ko Gen Surovikin ari "ruburakigongwe imbere y’umwansi”  - aho afata abarwanyi n’abasivire co kimwe
 Zirongowe n’uyu mu jenerali, ingabo z’Uburusiya zagize uruhara mu gukingira ikibaba ikoreshwa ry’ubumara bwa sarin, nk’uko Lister aboviga
 Bariboneye ingene bwurizwa mu ndege ya Syria iminota mike imbere y’igitero c’ubumara cihaye inkumbi mu gisagara ca  Khan Sheikhoun, aho abantu barenga 80 bapfuye
 Mu 2017 Perezida Putin yambitse Gen Surovikin ikidari c’Intwari y’Uburusiya  - ikidari gikuru gusumba ibindi vyose mu gihugu – kubera ivyo yakoze muri Syria, mu gihe ishirahamwe Human Rights Watch ryamushize ku rutonde rw’abashobora gukurikiranwa kw’ihonyangwa ry’agateka ka zina muntu
 Mu bihe bitari bike, abasirikare bari barongowe na Gen Surovikin baragirijwe gukubagura abasivire
 Muri Tchétchénie, ababibonye bavuga ko abarwanyi bakoze ibikorwa vyo “gutema batongora” , aho imihana y’abasivire yabomaguwe nayo abanyagihugu barakubitwa, nk’uko igisata ca BBC gikoresha ikirusiya kibivuga
 Gen Surovikin yariyamirije ivyo birego
 Mu myaka 30 canke irenga ivyo kwitwa "umuntu w’umugome, atoroshe kandi atawumuha nirwere” vyarabandanije, nk’uko Prof Waldron abivuga
 Ibi bibonekera haba ku rugamba canke mu buzima busanzwe
 Mu 2004, inyuma y’imyaka ibiri gusa arangije ivyigwa vy’intwazangabo kw’ishure rya gisirikare, Gen Surovikin avugwa ko yakubise umwe mu basirikare biwe kubera ivyiyumviro vyiwe vya poritike, nk’uko bivugwa n’ikigo cigisha ibijanye n’intambara
 Mu nyuma uyu musirikare yahavuye afutisha urubanza
 Ikinyamakuru Kommersant  cegamiye uruhande rwa reta y’Uburusiya canditse ko muri uyo mwaka nyene, Gen Surovikin yarengukishije umwe mu ba koroneri aramutuka
 Haciye akanya, uyo musirikare yarirashe arapfa
 None ni kubera iki Putin yamugenye? Prof Waldron avuga ko ari icerekana neza ko ibintu bitariko bigenda neza
 Yongerako ati: "Ntushobora guhindura uwurongoye urugamba kiretse ibintu bitariko bigenda uko vyateguwe”
 "Guhindura uwurongoye urugamba hano bishobora guhindura ibintu ariko ko hari ico bishobora guhindura mu bijanye n’ubushobozi nta wubizi”
 Kuba azwi ko ari umugome bishobora kutazana akarusho ku rubuga ariko bamwe bishimiye igenwa ryiwe
 Umukuru wa Tchétchénie/Chechnya Ramzan Kadyrov hamwe n’uwatanguje umurwi Wagner w’abacangero, Yevgeny Prigozhin – incuti zikomeye za Perezida Putin – baramushimagiza
 Prigozhin, umurwizatunga yataziriwe Umwishikira wa Putin, avuga ko uyu mujenerali ari yo “ntwazangabo ya mbere ishoboye ibikorwa” mu gisirikare c’Uburusiya
 Prof Waldron avuga ko ibi ari vyo vyatumye Putin agena uyu muntu
 Ati: "Ni umuntu azwi cane ko ari umugome
 Ubwo Putin yoba ariko agerageza gutanga ikimenyetso kuri Ukraine c’ukungene ashaka ko intambara ibandanya guhera ubu?”
Umugambwe uri ku butegetsi mu Bushinwa, umugambwe w’Abakomunista, witezwe kwemeza ikiringo kigira gatatu c’imyaka itanu ca prezida Xi Jinping, umutegetsi ata nkeka akomeye cane kuva kuri Mao Zedong mu myaka ya 1970
 Iyi ngingo – ije inyuma y’aho itegeko ryemera ibiringo bibiri rikuriweho mu 2018 – ishobora kumutuma yifatira neza na neza Ubushinwa
 Birashoboka ko Xi azoguma ku butegetsi mu kiringo cose asigaje co kuba kw’isi
 Iyi ngingo yitezwe gufatwa mw’ikoraniro kaminuza ry’umugambwe w’Abakomunista i Pékin/Beijing ritegekanijwe gutangura ku wa 16 Gitugutu (10)  - imwe mu nama nkuru nkuru z’uyu mugambwe muri kahise kawo
 Afatwa kandi nk’umutegetsi w’ikirenga
 Xi asa n’uwuzogumana izi ntebe zibiri za mbere, umunyamabanga mukuru w’umugambwe be n’umukuru w’Inama nkuru ya gisirikare muri iryo koraniro kaminuza ry’umugambwe – hamwe kandi n’ikibanza c’umukuru w’igihugu mw’Ikoraniro ry’umwaka ry’inama nshingamateka y’ico gihugu (National People's Congress) mu 2023
 Intumwa zababa 2300 zizohurira mu kibanza citiriwe Tiananmen Square's Great Hall of the People mu kiringo c’indwi yose
 Abashika  200 muri bo bazotorwa kugira baje muri komite nkuru y’umugambwe, hajeko n’abandi hafi   170 bashobora kuba abasubirizi
 Komite nkuru izotora abantu 25 baja mu biro bikuru
 Hanyuma ibiro bikuru navyo bitore abazogira komite ntayegayezwa mu biro bikuru
 Aba ni incabwenge zikuriye izindi
 Ubu iyi irimwo abantu indwi, harimwo n’umunyamabanga mukuru w’umugambe Xi Jinping
 Bose ni abagabo
 Si vyose bibera muri iyo nama kaminuza yo nyene
 Komite nkuru yiteze gukorana umusi umwe inyuma yo kurangira kw’iri koraniro kaminuza
 Xi azorongora iki gihugu kiza kabiri mu bihugu bitunze kw’isi kikongera kikaba kimwe mu bihugu bifise igisirikare gikomeye
 Bamwe mu bihweza ibintu n’ibindi bavuga ko ashobora kurongora Ubushinwa abuganisha mu butegetsi bw’agahotoro mu kiringo kigira gatatu c’imyaka itanu
 Umwigisha wa kaminuza Steve Tsang  wo kw’ishure kaminuza  London University's School of Oriental and African Studies (SOAS), avuga ati: "Ubushinwa kuri Xi buriko bwinjira mu ntwaro y’agahotoro”
 "Ubushinwa kuri Mao bwari ubutegetsi bw’agahotoro
 Ntiturahashika, ariko ni yo dutera tuja"
 Prof
 Tsang avuga ko iri koraniro kaminuza rishobora kuzana impinduka mw’itegeko mbumbarugo ry’uyu mugambwe, icitwa “Xi Jinping thought” (ni ukuvuga Ivyiyumviro vya  Xi Jinping ) gishobora kugirwa akarangamutima k’umugambwe
 "Xi Jinping thought" ni ko karanga ka Xi kuri socialism y’Ubushinwa, intwaro iterekwa na gato igisata c’abikorera utwabo
 Ku ntwaro yiwe, abategetsi b’Ubushinwa barahize buhongo amakompanyi akomakomeye mu bisata bitari bike vy’ubutunzi bw’igihugu
 Prof Tsang  ati: "Mu gihe ibi vyoba, nta nkeka ko bizomugira umutegetsi atwaza agahotoro”
 Abagize ubutegetsi bw’Ubushinwa, aba nabo bakazoshirwa ahabona muri iryo koraniro kaminuza, bazoshiraho imigambi ngenderwako itari mike
 Ikintu ico ari co cose cerekana kazoza k’Ubushinwa kizokurikiranirwa hagufi kw’isi yose, cane cane ku bibazo nkoramutima: ubutunzi, poritike, imigenderanire n’ibidukikije
 Ubutunzi bw’Ubushinwa bwariyongereye cane muri ino myaka mirongo iheze
 Ariko muri kino gihe buhanganye n’ihungabana rikomeye ry’ubutunzi ryavuye ku ngingo za guma mu rugo kubera Covid, ivyatumye ibiciro vyiyongera, n’ifaranga ry’igihugu rikaja mu ngorane zikomeye
 Ubwoba bubandanya ko ubutunzi bw’isi bushobora kuzama kubera intambara yo muri Ukraine nabwo nyene bwaratumye icizere kigabanuka
 Ku ntwaro ya Xi, ubutunzi bw’igihugu bwagiye hasi ugereranije n’ubwo ku bakuru b’igihugu b’imbere yiwe Jiang Zemin na Hu Jintao
 Bamwe mu bihweza ibintu n’ibindi bavuga ko ubutegetsi bwa gikomunista bwemewe bushingiye cane ku bushobozi bwabwo bwo gutanga amafaranga menshi ndetse n'akazi keza ku bakozi b'Abashinwa
 Rero mu gihe ubutunzi bwokwifata nabi mu myaka itanu iri imbere bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi za poritike kuri Xi
 Iri koraniro kaminuza rizotegura inzira z’impinduka mu bisata bikomakomeye vy’ubutunzi harimwo no mw’ibanki nkuru y’igihugu
 Poritike y’Ubushinwa ya Covid zero mu kurwanya iki kiza ni imwe muri poritike shingiro za Xi
 Mu gihe ibihugu bitari bike biriko birasubira mu buzima busanzwe, abategetsi b’Ubushinwa bobo  barongereje inguvu mu ntumbero yo kurwanya iki kiza, mu gufata amategeko ruhasha ya guma mu rugo, gupima abantu benshi ica rimwe, hamwe n’imisi myinshi yo kwitaramura
 Amakuru avuga ko ibisagara birenga 70 harimwo Shenzen na Chengdu, bimaze igihe mu ngingo za guma mu rugo mu ndwi nkeya ziheze, aho amamiriyoni mirongo y’ababibamwo bagizweko ingaruka, ibikorwa vyinshi vy’ubudandaji birapfa mbere hakaba hari n’amakuru avuga ko abanyagihugu bafise agashavu
 Xi yariyemeje “gutuza n’inguvu ziwe zose amajambo n’ibikorwa vyose bisambura, biteza amadidane canke bihakana” poritike yiwe kuri Covid
 Mu gihe hokwaduka ikiza muri kino gihe co kwitegurira iri koraniro kaminuza, canke mu gihe c’ikoraniro nyezina, kirashobora gucafuza isura ya Xi
 Bamwe mu bihweza ibintu n’ibindi bavuga ko umugambwe ushobora gukoresha iri koraniro mu gutangaza intsinzi kuri iki kiza ugaca uhagarika poritike ya Covid Zero
 Atari uko naho, umugambwe ushobora kuvuga ko Ubushinwa  - mu buryo butandukanye n’ibindi bihugu – buha agaciro ubuzima bw’abanyagihugu gusumba ubutunzi, ico gihe poritike igaca ibandanya
 Xi yashize imbere kandi gufata umurongo ukaze mu migenderanire n’Uburengero, cane cane ku kibazo ca Taiwan
 Urugendo umukuru w’inama nshingamateka ya Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yagize muri Taiwan mu kw’umunani rwatumye Ubushinwa butanguza imyimenyerezo ya gisirikare, harimwo no kurasa ibisasu vya misire, mu micungararo y’iryo zinga
 Ubushinwa bufata Taiwan nk’intara yabwo ishaka kwiyonkora kandi ko impera n’imperuka izoruhira kuganzwa na Pékin
 Taiwan yoyo yifata ko yigenga
 Xi avuga ko “gusubirana” na Taiwan “bitegerezwa kuzoba vyabaye” gushika mu 2049, imyaka ijana Repubulika y’Abanyagihugu izoba imaze – mbere ntishira ku ruhande ivyo gukoresha inguvu kugira bishikweko
 Abahinga mu vy’umutekano bavuga ko mu gihe Taiwan yokwigarurirwa n’Ubushinwa, ubwiganze Amerika ifise mu Nyanja ya Pasifike n’ahandi bwoba burangiye
 Taiwan ifitiye akamaro kadasanzwe Uburengero, kuko iri mu  citwa “urukurikirane rwa mbere rw’amazinga” (first island chain) rugizwe n’igitigiri c’amazinga yamye yunze ubumwe na Amerika kuva imyaka mirongo iheze

Tanzania iriko isaba amakungu n’amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu ko yoyifasha kugira ngo ishobore guhungura impunzi z’Abarundi zirenga 120
000
 Abegwa n’umugambi wo guhungurwa ni abari mu makambi yo mu ntara ya Kigoma ihana urubibe n’Uburundi, mu burengero bwa Tanzania
 Izi mpunzi ziri mu makambi ya Nduta na Nyarugusu zozo zivuga ko zimaze igihe zitorohewe kubera igitsure zivuga ko ziterwa kugira ngo zitahuke
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mw’ikoraniro rigira 73 ya komite nshingwabikorwa y’ishami rya ONU ryitaho impunzi kw’isi (UNHCR) i Geneva mu Buswisi, umushikiranganji ajejwe intwaro yo hagati wa Tanzania, Hamad Masauni, yavuze ko Uburundi bukeneye gufatwa mu mugongo mu ntumbero yo guhimiriza no kworohereza abashaka guhunguka ku bushake bwabo
 Ati: “Kugira ngo uwu mugambi ushoboke, ni ngombwa ko ibintu vyose bimera neza mu Burundi
 “Ikintu nyamukuru ni ugushigikira Uburundi kugira ngo abarondera ubuhungiro muri Tanzania bumve ko igihugu cabo ari bwo bukiriro bwabo”
 Mu myaka ya 2006 na 2007, Tanzania yarahaye ubwenegihugu impunzi zababa 160
000 ziri mu makambi ya Katumba, Ulyankulu na Mishamo mu ntara za Tabora na Katavi, harimwo impunzi zahunze indyane zo mu 1972, abatari bake usanga batazi iwabo mu Burundi
 Impunzi ziri mu makambi ya Kigoma zirwiriyemwo izahunze indyane za poritike zadutse mu 2015  biturutse ku ngingo y’uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu ico gihe, Perezida Petero Nkurunziza, yo kwitoreza ikiringo kigira gatatu
 Ariko abatari bake baramaze gutahuka mu mugambi wo guhungura impunzi ku bushake bwabo, ariko hari n’abandi babona ko hataragera ko bahunguka
 Mu gihe abatari bake muri bo bafise ubwoba ko bashobora guhungurwa ku nguvu, reta ya Tanzania yoyo gushika ubu ivuga ko umugambi wo guhungura impunzi ubu ukorwa ku bushake bwabo
 Hagati aho, impunzi zivuga ko imigambi zafatiwe mu makambi be n’amajambo zibwirwa n’abategetsi batandukanye b’iki gihugu kibahaye indaro bitabahumiriza
 Babona ko bashobora guhungurwa ku nguvu mu gihe bo babona hatari bwagere ko bahunguka, kuko bavuga ko ubutegetsi bahunze ari bwo bugihari
 Umwe mu mpunzi wo mw'ikambi ya Nduta yabwiye BBC ati: “Ntitwanka igihugu, kuko nico catuvyaye, ariko ntidushaka kuja kwisuka ku risongoye
 "Dusaba ko izi nguvu bagomba gukoresha mu kuduhungura ku nguvu ko bozijana mu Burundi bakagondoza irya reta kugira ngo ishireho icizere, maze dushobora gutahuka ata bwoba”

