 Impande zompi zarumvikanye kwitaba ibiganiro vy’amahoro muri Afrika y’Epfo, kandi umuganga atakamba asaba ko akaga kugarije abantu koja mu bibazo vya mbere vyo kwiga no gutorera inyishu
 Muganga Fasika Amdeslasie avuga nk’uko umenga ntaco bimubwiye, ariko ivyo avuga biteye akoba
 “Dukenye imiti yo gutimbisha (gutera ikinya), dukenye serumu, ntihagira antibiotique, niho rero ububona indwara zikomera, mu nyuma abarwayi bagapfa ata gitabara - uzinze amaboko”
 Uwo muganga ivyo yabivuze ahamagawe kuri Whatsapp kuri internet ya satellite, imbonekarimwe ku murwa mukuru wa Tigray, Mekelle
 Abarwayi ntibagira uko bagira, ariko n’abaganga nico kimwe
 Yamara, ariko arakuyagira ingaruka z’intambara ku gisata c’amagara y’abantu aho muri Tigray, Muganga Fasika, akora ku bitaro bikuru vya Ayder ku murwa mukuru Mekelle, mu maso ntiwomenya ko ariko aravuga ibintu bibabaje
 Mu kiringo c’imyaka ibiri iheze, Tigray ntizi ibibera ahandi kw’isi
 Intambara yatanguye muri Munyonyo (11) mu  2020 igihe ingabo za reta ya Ethiopia zarondera kwaka ubutegetsi bw’iyo ntara umugambwe TPLF (Tigray People’s Liberation Front)
 Intara ya Tigray yaciye yugaranwa rwose igihe TPLF yatunganya igitero ikisubiza igice kinini c'iyo ntara muri Ruheshi mu 2021
 Nta bintu bishobora kwinjira, banki zarahagaze, terefone nazo ziracibwa ku buryo bidashoboka guhamagara umuntu muri iyo ntara
 ONU igereranya ko abantu bangana na miriyoni 5
4 – hafi batatu kuri bane mu bantu bose baba muri Tigray – bakeneye imfashanyo y’ivyo kurya kuko intambara yahungabanije uruhererakane rw’ivyo kurya
 N’abarwayi ntagahengwe bagirirwa, n’ubwo bo ata ruhara bafise mu rugamba
 Hari imiti n’ibikoresho nkoramutima vyazanwe n’ishami rya ONU ryitaho amagara kw’isi hamwe na CICR – ariko iza ryayo ryagiye riba ahandi ntiribe, noneho ibintu birahagarra rwose igihe intanbara zasubira kwaduka muri Myandagaro (8), inyuma y’agahengwe k’amezi atanu
 Dr Fasika  yabwiye ikiganiro ca BBC Newsday ati: “Nta miti y’abarwayi bacu dufise, ntitugira ibikoresho vyo kubaga, nta ncanco (inkingo) dufise zo gukingira abana,  nta insuline dufise yo guha abarwaye diabete
” “Abarwayi bose nta gahengwe
 Tubabwira gusubira imuhira iwabo tutabavuye
” Imiti yo kuvura abarwaye cancer ntiboneka namba, kandi ntibashobora kugirirwa ‘radiotherapie’ kuko imashini yo kubikora iri ku murwa mpuzantaray, Addis Ababa
 Kugendayo ntibishoboka
 “Muri make, abarwayi bacu bategerezwa gupfa,” nk’uko bivugwa n’uwo muganga w’imyaka 41 yigeze kuba umukuru w’ishure ry’ubuganga
 Abavuzi baguma baraba aho abarwaye amafyigo amagara yabo aguma yunyuka kuko imiti yo gukora dialyse ija iraboneka yongera ibura
 Ku bwa Muganga Fasika, “Imiti ya nyuma yaje muri Ruheshi (6),  kuva muri Myandagaro (8) nta kintu na kimwe casubiye kwinjira none ubu ibikoresho vyaduheranye ku barwayi  25 dufise”
 Avuga ko abarwayi b’amafyigo 90 bapfuye “bari imbere y’abaganga” akibaza ibigiye gushikira abo 25 basigaye
 Ku bijanye no gupima, icumba co gupima (laboratoire) ntikigira imiti ikenewe mu gupima, akenshi abaganga bakaba batamenya neza ingorane umurwayi aba afise
 Kuri ivyo vyose hiyongerako ingorane z’umuyagankuba ukunda gucikagurika mu gihe ata bitoro bihari vyo gushira mu moteri zitanga umuyagankuba
 Bisigura ko ibitaro bishobora kumara iminsi biri mu kizime
 Muri urwo rusobekerane rw’ingorane we n’abo bakorana barimwo, ijwi rya Muganga Fasika ntiriserura uburemere bw’ivyo ariko aravuga
 ”Naraheze ibishobisho, bisigaye ari ubuzima bwa minsi yose, ndiko mvuga ivyo mbamwo ku munsi ku munsi
 ”Turirinda gutwarwa n’ibishobisho
 Tuzomenya umutwaro twiremetse umunsi twavuye  muri ibi
 Ubundi ni kamere k’umuntu ko kwirwanako kutavyibaza, ivyo urabireka ugakora ivyo ushoboye gukora
” Ariko abaganga n’abaforoma, co kimwe n’abakozi ba reta, bahanganye no kuba badahembwa kuva mu kwezi kwa Rusama (5)
 Muganga Fasika arungikirwa amafaranga n’abagenzi n’incuti bari mu mahanga ariko, ivyo bitwara amafaranga menshi kuko abayavunja bakurako menshi kuko bategerezwa kuyinjiza mu mpisho muri Tigray
 Muganga Fasika avuga ko “ibi bitaro ari ubuzima bwanje”, agasigura ikimutera kubandanya akora n’aho ahanzwe n’ibibazo vyinshi
 “Umwuga uraguhamagara
 Iyo ushoboye kugenda ukayagisha abarwayi ukabaha impanuro hanyuma ugakora ivyo ushoboye, ico nico kintu gihambaye
 Si jewe gusa, n’abandi bose dukorana ngaha
” Ku kibazo c’ibiganiro bishobora kuba hagati ya reta mpuzantara na TPLF, Muganga Fasika ntashaka kuvuga poritike
 Ariko arajwe ishinga n’uko mu gihe ibiganiro ari igikorwa ca poritike, bazoguma mu ngorane mu gihe vyo bishobora kumara igihe imbere y’uko hari ico bishikako
 “Ibiganiro bishobora gufata umwanya
