Ivyago vyo kubona isi iguye mu kaga ka nikleyeri katari bwigere kabaho biri ku rugero runini kuva kuri ca gihe ca misire za Cuba (Crise des missiles de Cuba/ Cuban Missile Crisis)  mu 1962, nk’uko Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika abivuga
 Biden avuga ko Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya atariko “arayayata” igihe avuga ko ashobora gukoresha ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri (vy’ubumara) inyuma y’aho atakarije bikomeye ku rubuga rw’intambara muri Ukraine
 Yongerako y’uko Amerika “iriko irihweza” inzira Putin ashobora gufata mu kwikura mu ntambara
 Amerika n’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya biherutse kuvuga ko iterabwoba rya Putin kw’ikoreshwa ry’ibirwanisho vy’ubumara atari iryo gufata minenerwe
 Hagati aho, umuhanuzi wa Amerika mu vyo umutekano Jake Sullivan yavuze mu ndwi iheze ko, n’aho Moscou yacishije mu kanwa ivy’ibirwanisho vy’ubumara, Amerika ata bimenyetso ibona ko Uburusiya bushobora kuba buriko bwitegurira gukoresha ikirwanisho c’ubumara
 Ukraine imaze imisi ibohoza ubutaka bwari bwigaruriwe n’Uburusiya kuva butanguye igitero cabwo ku wa 24 z’ukwa kabiri, harimwo n’intara zine Uburusiya buherutse kwihagira mu buryo buteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Haraciye amezi atari make abategetsi ba Amerika bagabisha ko Uburusiya bushobora kwikora ku birwanisho ruhonyanganda mu gihe bwobona ko buriko buratakaza ku rugamba
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije ku wa gatanu w’indwi iheze, Putin yavuze ko Amerika ari yo “ntandaro ya vyose” mu gukoresha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara ku Buyapani mu mpera z’intambara ya kabiri y’isi yose – amajambo atari kugenda gutyo nyene mu bihugu vy’Uburengero, nk’uko bivugwa n’umwanditsi mukuru wa BBC mu rurimi rw’ikirusiya, Steve Rosenberg
 Putin kandi yagabishije ko azokoresha uburyo bwose afise kugira ngo akingire ubutaka bw’Uburusiya
 Perezida Biden avuga ko igituma umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya “atariko arafyinata” igihe avuga ivyo gukoresha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara, ari uko “igisirikare ciwe, nk’uko twobivuga, kiriko kiraneshwa”
 Biden yabwiye bagenziwe bo mu mugambwe w’aba Democrats ati: "Ubwa mbere kuva ku kibazo ca misire za Cuba, turi imbere y’ivyago vy’ikoreshwa ry’ibirwanisho vy’ubumara, mu gihe ibintu vyobandanya uko biri”
 “Ntitwari bwigere twibaza ko dushobora guhangana n’icago kiruta ibindi vyose kuva kuri Kennedy n’ikibazo ca misire za Cuba”
 Mu 1962, Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hamwe n’Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti  - ico gihe hari ku ba perezida John F Kennedy na Nikita Khrushchev – vyahatswe guterana ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri (vy’ubumara) biturutse ku ngingo y’Ubumwe bw’abasoviyeti yo kurungika ibirwanisho vy’ubumara muri Cuba
 Abahinga batari bake babona ko iri hangana ari ryo ryonyene rikomeye ryahatswe guta isi mu ntambara ya nikleyeri
 Biden yabwiye bagenziwe b’aba Democrats ko ikoreshwa ry’ibirwanisho vy’ubumara bishobora gutuma ibintu biyangara mu kanya isase
 Yavuze ibi ari ku muhana wa James Murdoch i New York, umuhungu w’umutunzi karuhariwe Rupert Murdoch azwi ko yashoye imitahe myinshi mu gisata co kumenyesha amakuru, hari mu birori vyo kwegeranya uburyo bw’umugambwe w’aba-Democrats
 Putin ahanganye n’ishusho igoye cane ku rugamba
 N’aho yateye igikumu kw’itegeko ryihagira burundu intara zine za Ukraine - Luhansk, Donetsk, Zaporizhzhia na Kherson – ingabo za Kyiv ziriko zirasatira zinjira muri utwo turere avuga ko twamwegukiye
 Ibihumbi amajana vy’abagabo bariko barahunga Uburusiya hako barindira ngo bandikwe kugira bajanwe kurwana muri Ukraine
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky  wa Ukraine yahoze afata minenerwe iterabwoba rya nikleyeri rya Moscou, akavuga ko ari "amajambo yo kwiyamamaza yama avugwa n’abategetsi b’Uburusiya”
 Paul Stronski, wo mw’ishirahamwe Carnegie Endowment for International Peace, yabwiye BBC ko “amajambo y’iterabwoba” y’Uburusiya afise intumbero yo gukanga Uburengero, n’aho Uburengero busa n’ubwiyemeje guhangana naryo
 Eka mbere no mu Burusiya nyene ubwabwo hari abarwanya iri terabwoba rya Moscou rishingiye ku birwanisho vy’ubumara
 Inkuru yo mu kinyamakuru Nezavisimaya Gazeta co muri ico gihugu iranegura cane “abategetsi bakuru b’Uburusiya” kubera “ bakinisha ivya nikleyeri”
 "Kwemera, haba mu vyiyumviro canke mu majambo,  y’uko hashobora kuba intambara ya nikleyeri ni intambwe ikomeye yo kuyitanguza mu vy’ukuri”
 Umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bw’Uburusiya bujejwe imigenderanire yabwiye abanyamakuru ejo ku wa kane ko Moscou itari bwahindure aho ihagaze, ko intambara ya nikleyeri ari “ikizira kikaziririzwa”

Ales Bialiatski n’umunya-Belarus azwi cane mu kugwanira agateka ka zina muntu, ubu apfunzwe ata rubanza yaciriwe
 Uwo mugabo w’imyaka 60 niwe yashinze ikigo co guharanira agateka ka zina muntu citwa Viasna, catanguye mu 1996 inyuma y’ihashwa ry’imyiyerekano yo mu mabarabara  n’umutegetsi w’igitugu wa Belarus Alexander  Lukashenko
 Viasna catanze ubufasha ku bari mu myiyerekano bari bafashwe bagapfungwa no ku miryango yabo, gikora amatohoza ku kuboreza igufa (iyicarubozo) abapfungiwe poritike bakorerwa n’abategetsi ba Belarus
 Umukuru  wa komite yo muri Norvege itanga agashimwe ka Nobel Berit Reiss-Andersen yavuze ko “yihebeye guteza imbere demokrasi n’iterambere ry’amahoro mu gihugu ciwe” igihe yariko aratangaza batatu batsindiye ako gashimwe k’amahoro uyu mwaka
 Bialiatski – asanzwe yari amaze kuronka utundi dushimwe twinshi mpuzamakungu –  yamaze imyaka itatu apfunzwe inyuma yo kwagirwa n’ivyaha vyo  gukwepa kuriha amakori, ivyaha yagumye ahakana mu 2011
 Yerekuwe mu 2014
 Yasubiye gupfungwa mu 2020 inyuma y’imyiyerekano ikomeye cane kubera ico abatavuga rumwe na reta bise amatora yibwe muri Belarus bigatuma Lukashenko aguma ku butegetsi
 Madame Reiss-Andersen yagize ati: Abategetsi ba reta  bagumye barondera buri igihe gucecekesha Ales Bialiatski”
 “N’ubwo ubwiwe yagumye ahura n’amagume akomeye, Bialiatski ntiyigeze adohoka na gato ku rugamba rwiwe rwo kurwanira agateka ka zina muntu na demokrasi muri Belarus
” Imbere gato y’uko afatwa haraheze imyaka ibiri, Bialiatski yanditse ku rubuga rwiwe rwa Facebook ko abategetsi ba Belarus “bakora nk’uko umenga  n’intwaro yaje kwigarurira igihugu”
 “Ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’abantu bagize imyiyerekano mu gihugu cose, kandi amajana n’amajana [muri bo] barapfunzwe
” Ingene amagara ya Bialiatski yifashe ubu ntibizwi
 Lukashenko – afatwa  mu bihugu vy’iburengerazuba nk’umunyagitugu wa nyuma w’i Buraya- atwaza umukazo Belarus kuva mu 1994
 Yemereye umukuru w’Uburusiya Vladimir Putin, basanzwe bacuditse cane, gukoresha ubutaka bwa Belarus mu kugaba ibitero vya misire vyishe benshi muri Ukraine no mu kurungika ingabo z’Uburusiya zo ku butaka n’ibiduga vy’intambara muri ico gihugu kuva ku munsi wa mbere Uburusiya butera ku  wa 24 Ruhuhuma (ukwezi kwa kabiri)
 H﻿amwe na Bialiatski, ikigo co muri Ukraine giharanira agateka ka zina muntu  Center for Civil Liberties (CCL)  naco kiri muri batatu batsindiye ako gashimwe
 Ako gashimwe kahawe kandi ikigo co mu Burusiya c'ageteka ka zina muntu Memorial - cugwawe n'abategetsi uyu mwaka

