N﻿a Jean Mackenzie & Frances Mao Abanyamakuru ba BBC Seoul Korea ya Ruguru yarashe ibindi bisasu vya misire bibiri kuri uno wa kane  - ikaba ibaye incuro/inshuro ya gatandatu igerageza ibi bisasu bibujijwe mu kiringo kiri musi y’indwi zibiri
 Ejo ku wa gatatu, Pyongyang (umugwa mukuru wa Korea ya Ruguru) yavuze ko kurekura ibi bisasu ari “ingingo zo kwihora” imyimenyerezo rusangi ya Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika na Korea y’Epfo
 Ku wa kabiri, Pyongyang yarashe igisasu ca misire hejuru y’Ubuyapani, ivyatumye Amerika isaba inama yihuta y’Inama Nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano
 Muri iyi nama, Amerika yagirije Uburusiya n’Ubushinwa ko bukingira Korea ya Ruguru kugira ntifatirwe ibihano ruhasha
 Uwuserukira Amerika muri ONU avuga ko mu kwanka ibindi bihano, Uburusiya n’Ubushinwa “biyaye impigi” Pyongyang
 Abaserukira ibi bihugu bibiri ntayegayezwa mu Nama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano bavuga ko gukomeza ibiganiro ari yo nzira nziza gusumba ibihano
 Mu mezi abiri aheze, Amerika, Korea y’Epfo n’Ubuyapani vyakoreye hamwe imyimenyerezo rusangi mu ntumbero yo kwimenyereza gutsinda no gutesha igitero cova muri Korea ya Ruguru
 Iyi myimenyerezo yashavuje indongozi ya Korea ya Ruguru Kim Jong-un, ayibonamwo nk’icemezo ko abansi biwe bariko bitegurira intambara
 Mw’itangazo, Korea ya Ruguru yagiriza Amerika gutuma “icuka kibi kirangwa kuri ico kigwa ca Korea mu rwego rwa gisirikare cunyuka”
 Ejo ku wa gatatu, Amerika, Korea y’Epfo n’Ubuyapani vyarabandanije imyimenyerezo, bivuga ko yari iyo kwihora Korea ya Ruguru ku gisasu yari yateye ku wa kabiri
 Amerika kandi yasubiye kurungika ubwato butwara indege z’intambara USS Ronald Reagan hafi y’ikigwa ca Korea
 Korea y’Epfo n’Ubuyapani bivuga ko igisasu ca mbere ca misire zarashwe kuri uno wa kane cashitse ku birometero 350, congera kigera ku burebure bw’ibirometero 100 uja hejuru, mu gihe ica kabiri cari kuguruka gushika ku birometero 800 be no ku birmetero vyababa 50 uja hejuru
 Uru rukurikirane rw’ibisasu biherutse kuraswa rwibutsa igihe c’imbere y’igerageza rya nyuma ry’ikirwanisho c’ubumara mu 2017
 Ico gihe, nk’uko biriko biragenda ubu, Korea ya Ruguru yagerageje ibisasu vya misire, nta biganiro na Amerika vyari bwabe, hanyuma Pyongyang itera ibisasu bibiri vya misire hejuru y’Ubuyapani
 Amasanamu y’ibigendajuru yerekana ko Korea ya Ruguru iriko irasanura imyobo yayo yo ku kigo c’igeragerezo ry’ibirwanisho vya nikleyeriyari yavuga ko yasambuye mu 2018 igihe haba ibiganiro vy’akanya gato na Amerika ku ntwaro ya Perezida Trump
 Mu kwezi guheze, Korea ya Ruguru yasubiyemwo amategeko yayo ajanye na nikleyeri, aho indongozi yayo Kim Jong Un yatangaje ko igihugu ciwe kigiye ku rutonde rw’ibihugu bitunze ibirwanisho vy’ubumara “ubutagisubira inyuma”
 Mu gihe ubu ibintu vyose bitunganye, Kim asa n’uwurindiriye akanya keza ka poritike kugira ngo agerageza ikindi gisasu ca nikleyeri ku ncuro igira indwi
 Abihweza ibintu n’ibindi babona ko igikorwa co kugerageza iki gisasu gishobora kuba mu kadirisha k’indwi zitatu hagati y’ikoraniro kaminuza ry’umugambwe wa Gikomunista w’Ubushinwa mu mpera za kuno kwezi hamwe n’amatora y’abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka muri Amerika mu ntango za Munyonyo (11)

Abana barenga 150 bari bafise ingwara y'amaraso atavura  izwi nka haemophilia/hémophilie barandujwe umugera wa SIDA mu myaka ya 1980, nk’uko biri mu nyandiko z’ububiko bw’igihugu zabonywe na BBC
 Imwe mu miryango yahuye n’izi ngorane iravuga ingene vyagenze mu matohoza y’igihugu ku gifatwa ko ari akaga k’agahomerabunwa mu buganga muri kahise k’ikigo c’Ubwongereza kijejwe amagara y’abantu, NHS
 Haraciye imyaka hafi 36 – mu mpera z’ukw’icumi 1986 – ariko Linda ntazokwigera yibagira umusi abwirwa ko umwana wiwe w’umuhungu yari yandujwe umugera
 Ibitaro vy’abana vya Birmingham (Birmingham Children's Hospital), vyaramutumyeko, ari kumwe n’umwana wiwe w’umuhungu Michael yari afise imyaka 16
 Igihe yari acavura, yarapimwe asanga yari arwaye haemophilia, ingwara yo mu muryango ituma amaraso atavura neza
 Linda yibaza ko uwo mubonano wari ukuvugana ingene yokwungururizwa mu bitaro bikuru vyitiriwe Umwamikazi Elizabeth (Queen Elizabeth Hospital) muri ico gisagara
 Ati: "Vyari ibintu dusanzwe tumenyereye ku buryo umugabo wanje yigumiye mu modoka hanze
 "Ubwo nyene, nk’igitangaro, muganga yavuze ati, 'Ni vyo, Michael yaranduye umugera wa SIDA', kandi nyene yabivuze nk’uko umengo yariko aravuga ingene ikirere cifashe hanze
 Numvise ivyari mu nda bihiye
 "Twarinjiye mu modoka, ndabibwira umugabo wanje, duca turanuma gushika muhira
 Nta wigeze avuga – twakubiswe n’inkuba”
 Hari hakiri mu myaka ya mbere y’uwu mugera wa SIDA – hasigaye amezi make imbere y’uko isekeza rya reta ryacishwa ku mboneshakure ryiswe Don't Die of Ignorance (Ntiwicwe n’ukutamenya) ritangura kwigisha buri Mwongereza ivyerekeye iyi ngwara
 Ariko kunena umuntu yanduye uwu mugera vyari vyamaze kwisasira indava
 Mu 1985,  abavyeyi batari bake bari bamaze gukura abana babo mw’ishure ry’intango ryo muri Hampshire inyuma y’aho umwana w’imyaka icenda  - nawe nyene yari afise iyi ngwara ya haemophilia – apimiwe agasanga yaranduye umugera wa SIDA
 Michael ntiyashaka ko abagenzi biwe canke mu muryango babimenya
 Linda ati: "Uko niko yavyitwayemwo – yavyigumijemwo”
 "Ntiyigeze abwira na kimwe abagenzi biwe kuko yipfuza kubaho mu buzima busanzwe"
 Hagati ya 1970 na 1991, abantu 1250 bari bafise ibibazo vyo mu maraso barandujwe umugera wa SIDA  mu Bwongereza inyuma y’aho bafatiye umuti witwa Factor VIII – umuti mushasha wari uje gukoreshwa mu kuvura iyo ngorane
 Muri aba harimwo abana 175 bahawe uwu muti n’abaganga b’ikigo NHS mu bitaro, mu mashure canke mu bigo bivurirwamwo iyi ngwara ya haemophilia
 Abandi ibihumbi n’ibihumbi bavugwa ko bandujwe ingwara y’igitigu co mu bwoko bwa C (hépatite C/hepatitis C) ishobora gutuma igitigu cononekara canke kikagwara kanseri, haba mu kuvurwa iyi ngwara uku nyene canke mu guterwa amaraso
 Hafi igice c’abo bose bandujwe umugera wa SIDA barapfuye bishwe n’ingwara z’ivyuririzi imbere y’uko hatangura kuboneka imiti yo gupfupfahaza
 Ico gihe, Ubwongereza ntibwari bwikwije mu bubiko bw'amaraso aterwa abantu iyo bikenewe, rero uwo muti Factor VIII washika mu gihugu uvuye muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika
 Agapaki kamwe kamwe kaba kagizwe n’uruvange rw'amaraso yatanzwe n'ibihumbi vy'abantu
 Rero, iyo umwe muri bo yaba yaranduye umugera wa SIDA, waca ukwiragira hose
 Amakompanyi yahingura imiti muri Amerika yaraha amafaranga abantu kugira baze gutanga amaraso – kandi muri bo harimwo n’imirwi yari ifise ivyago vyinshi vyo gushobora kwandura, aha ni nk’abapfungwa canke abafata ibiyayuramutwe
 Linda aribuka igihe abwirwa ubwa mbere ivyerekeye SIDA mu nyigisho zabereye ku bitaro vy’abana vya Birmingham mu 1984 akanagabishwa ko yoza arihweza ibimenyetso bimwe bimwe
 Ariko avuga ko umuryango utigeze wigishwa neza akaga kawuhanze – igihe kimwe umuforoma yamubwiye ko atogira ubwoba, ko “Michael yari ameze neza”
 Ico gihe cose, umuhungu wiwe yabandanije avurwa hakoreshejwe uwo muti wari wavuye muri Amerika
 Mu mpera z’imyaka y’ubusore bwiwe, Michael yatanguye kugira ibibazo vy’amagara – guhera ku kubira icuya mw’ijoro  gushika aho atangura kumeneka umutwe hanyuma agafatwa n’igicurane
 Ariko yabandanije abaho mu buzima busanzwe  - afata ingendo, yumviriza umuziki mbere abandanya ashigikira umurwi w’umupira w’amaguru, West Bromwich Albion
 Linda ati: "Ico gihe hari urukino rukomeye ku kibuga ca Wembley kandi ico gihe yari ameze nabi, nabi cane”
 "Rero twararyohoye imodoka yose hanyuma aragenda guhura n’abagenzi biwe
 Uko yiyumva ntaco vyari bitwaye, ashoboye gushikayo, nta ngorane”
 Mu nyuma mu buzima bwiwe, abasoda b’umubiri batanguye kugabanuka, Michael yaratakaje ibiro, atangura kwumva uburuhe, n’ubwonko buratakara
 Yahavuye yungururizwa mu bitaro vya Heartlands muri Birmingham, ari naho Linda, inyuma yo guheba akazi kiwe k’ubuyaya mu kigo c’abakukuruke, yabandanije amufashiriza n’aho yari mu mezi make yiwe ya nyuma y’ubuzima bwiwe
 Linda ati: "Yambwiye ati, 'Mama, ntuzigera uba inakuru', nanje mvuga nti, 'Ntugire ingorane kuri ico’
 Ico nico nashoboye kwiyumvira nari kuvuga”
 Michael yafashwe na mugiga be n’umusonga – zompi zatewe n’umugera wa SIDA  yandujwe akiri umwana
 Yahavuye apfa ku wa 26 Rusama (5), 1995, hasigaye neza na neza indwi imwe gusa ngo agire isabukuru y’imyaka 26 y’amavuka
 Inyuma y’imyaka hafi 30, Linda aratanga ivyemezo kuri ano matohoza y’igihe kirekire kuri kano kaga kabaye mu buvuzi
 Azorenguka ari kumwe n’abandi bavyeyi, mu nama idasanzwe ijanye nivyo imiryango yaciyemwo mu kubona abana babo banduzwa umugera mu myaka ya 1970 na 1980
 Ati: ''Numva ko ari ngombwa ko ndabikora kuko nshaka gufasha kugira ngo ukuri kumenyekane”
 "Twese dushaka kumenya igituma baretse bikaba kandi bikabandanya uko nyene”
 Linda yasavye ko izina ryiwe ry’umuryango rinyegezwa
Ingabo za Ukraine zabohoje ikigwati gikomeye co mu ntara ya Kherson iri mu bumanuko, bituma abasirikare b’Uburusiya bongera gusubira inyuma vyihuta
 Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bwa Kyiv bwasohoye videwo yerekana brigade ya 35 y’abasirikare barwanira mu mazi iduza ibendera rya Ukraine mu kigwati ca Davydiv Brid, mu gihe hari ayandi makuru avuga ko ibindi bigwati bitari bike vyo mu micungararo biriko birafatwa
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya ziramaze kwirukanwa mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine, ubu naho zikaba zisubizwa inyuma no mu bumanuko
 Uku gutsindwa kw’ingabo z’Uburusiya kwaje mu gihe Perezida Vladimir Putin yari yiteze gutera igikumu kw’itegeko-bwirizwa ryihagira intara zine za Ukraine, mu gihe intambara zikibica bigacika muri izo zine zose
 Iyi ngendo yo kwihagira ubutaka bwa Ukraine iteye kubiri n’amategeko mpuzamakungu, mbere Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko ata gaciro ifise
 Perezida Joe Biden yaravuganye na Zelensky ejo ku wa kabiri amwemerera ko Amerika idashobora na gato kwemera ko Uburusiya bwihagira ubutaka bwa Ukraine
 Bavuganye kandi ku mfashanyo ya Amerika ingana n’imiriyoni 625 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika, zirimwo n’inkoho zo mu bwoko bwa Himars zirasa vya muzinga
 Uburusiya buracagenzura igisagara ca Kherson, umugwa mukuru w’intara, mu bumanuko
 Ariko uko bukeye uko bwije buboneka ko buriko buratakaza akarere ko mu buraruko bw’uruzi Dnieper, canke Dnipro nk’uko abanya-Ukrane barwita
 Mu masaha 48 aheze, ingabo za Ukraine zarasatiriye zija mu bumanuko, mu burengero bw’uru ruzi, bituma ingabo z’Uburusiya ziheba ibirindiro bitari bike mu buraruko bwa Kherson zigasubira nyuma
 Zelensky avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zasatiriye “ku muvuduko munini kandi ukomeye” mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine zibohoza “uturere tutari duke” muri ino ndwi yonyene
 Buciye ku mbuga hwaniro, ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bwa Ukraine bwanditse buti: "Ibendera rya Ukraine ryasubiye guhungabana mu kigwati ca Davydiv Brid"
 Abanyagihugu bahaba bafashe amashusho y’abasirikare ba Ukraine bariko barakizura muri ico kigwati
 Mw’ijambo yaraye ashikirije ku mugoroba w’ejo ku wa kabiri, Zelensky yavuze ko ibigwati vya Lyubimivka, Khreshchenivka, Zolota Balka, Bilyaivka, Ukrainka, Velyka Oleksandrivka na Mala Oleksandrivka navyo nyene  vyabohojwe, kandi ko atari ivyo gusa
 Icegera c’umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe intwaro yo hagati Yevhen Enin avuga ko ibisagara n’ibigwati 50 vyabohojwe, abanyagihugu bababa 3
500 na bo nyene baravanwa "mu minwe y’umwansi" muri Kherson, ariko ntiyavuze igihe ibi vyabereye
 Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi mu nyuma bwavuze ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zacitse intege zica zitangura kugerageza kubomora ibiraro kugira ngo zigabanye umurindi w’ingabo za Ukraine
 Umutegetsi wo muri Kherson yashizweho na Kremlin, Kirill Stremousov, yabwiye abanyagihugu ati: "Nta mpamvu yo kugira ubwoba"
 Ntivyashotse vyemezwa ko ibigwati biri mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Davydiv Brid navyo nyene vyisubijwe, mbere n’umuvugizi w’igisirikare c’Uburusiya ntiyigeze avuga ivyo gutakaza muri aco karere
 Ariko ku makarata yerekana ubutaka bugenzurwa n’Uburusiya, vyaboneka neza ko butakigenzura ibigwati vya Arkhanhelske na Velyka Oleksandrivka mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw’iyi ntara, hamwe na Dudchany ku nkengera y’uruzi Dnieper
 Umwanditsi wo ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi rw’igisirikare c’Uburusiya Rybar avuga ko igisirikare cafashe ingingo yo gusubira inyuma kubera cari guhava cugaranwa
 Icegera c’umukuru w’igisagara ca Kherson yahunze, Roman Holovnia, avuga ati: "Uduce dutuwemwo n’abantu tutari duke twarasambuwe – uduce tumwe tumwe nta nzu n’imwe igihagaze”
 Yongerako y’uko abanyagihugu bo muri ico gisagara barindiriye ingabo za Ukraine, kuko bazi ko ziriko zirasatira
 Ku bantu 320
000 baba muri ico gisagara imbere y’intambara, 100
000 bonyene nibo basigayeyo, nk’uko Holovnia abivuga
 Ingabo za Ukraine zimaze amayinga zitera amayira Uburusiya bukoresha mu gushikana vya nkenerwa ku rugamba mu karere ka Kherson, zisambura ibiraro vyari bisanzwe ari na bike kuri urwo ruzi
 Ariko mu bumanuko izi ngabo zigenda bukebuke
 Kherson yafashwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya mu kanya isase mu ntango y’intambara, igihe zinjira muri iyo ntara ziturutse mu karere ka Crimée/Crimea kigaruriwe mu 2014
 Ukraine yateye intambwe zikomeye i Kharkiv mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko be no muri Donetsk, aho ku wa gatandatu zigaruriye igisagara gikomeye ca Lyman
 Iki ni igisagara kiri mu ntara ya Donetsk ariko gifatwa ko ari irembo ryo kwinjira muri Luhansk, intara igice kinini cayo kiri mu minwe y’Uburusiya
 Umunyamakuru wa BBC Orla Guerin ari i Lyman, avuga ko hasigayeyo abasivire bakeya ubu, mu gihe ibiziga vy’ingabo z’Uburusiya bitari bike mu mwambaro wa gisirikare wazo bikirambaraye hanze y’igisagara
 Kherson, Luhansk, na Donetsk ziri mu ntara zigaruriwe n’Uburusiya mu buryo buteye kubiri n’amategeko, ariko biriko biboneka ko Vladimir Putin yihuse kuririmba intsinzi mu birori vyo ku wa gatanu vyo gutera igikumu kw’itegeko ryemeza ko Uburusiya bwihagiye izi ntara
 Umwanditsi wo ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi w’umurusiya yasohoye ibishingantahe vy’abagabo babiri avuga ko ari abarwanyi bo mu nyeshamba za Luhansk zifashwe mu mugongo n’Uburusiya, bavuga ko hahatswe gato ngo bazibirirwe hafi ya Lyman mu ndwi iheze
 Umwe muri aba bagabo yitwa Mikhei  avuga ati: "Twaravuye muri Lyman, ariko twavuyeyo uku nyene – ata n’urusasu dutwaye, ata na kimwe
 Vyose vyaraturiwe
 Incuti n’abagenzi bacu bose baguyeyo”
 Uburusiya gushika ubu bumaze kwinjiza ingabo nshasha zirenga 200
000 kuva Perezida Putin atanze integeko ryo kwinjiza abandi mu kwezi guheze, nk’uko umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi Sergei Shoigu abimenyesha
 Mu ntango bategura kwinjiza abantu 300
000, ariko iki gikorwa cagiye gihura n’ingorane z’amakuru avuga Abarusiya bagerageza guhunga iyi ngingo canke bahabwa ibikoresho ata kigenda iyo binjiye
 Igihugu ca Kazakhstan conyene kivuga ko Abarusiya barenga 200
000 bamaze kwinjira ku butaka bwaco mu ndwi zibiri ziheze

Korea y’Epfo n’igisirikare ca Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika vyarashe ibisasu vya misire bitari bike mu nyanja nk’uko bivugwa na Seoul, mu ntumbero yo kwihora Korea ya Ruguru yari yabiteye mu gaturuturu k’ejo ku wa kabiri hejuru y’Ubuyapani
 Izi misire zarashwe mu Nyanja y’Ubuseruko – izwi kandi nk’Inyanja y’Ubuyapani – hagati ya Korea n’Ubuyapani
 Ku wa kabiri, Pyongyang yarashe igisasu ca misire kiraswa kure mu bikorwa vyo kugerageza ibirwanisho vyayo, bukaba ari bwo bwa mbere yari igicishije hejuru y’Ubuyapani kuva mu 2017
 Mu kwihora, Amerika, Ubuyapani na Korea y’Epfo biri mu myimenyerezo rusangi mu ntumbero yo kwerekana inguvu zavyo
 Itangazo ryasohowe kuri uno wa gatatu, rivuga ko Korea y’Epfo na Amerika, kimwe kimwe cose carashe misire zo mu bwoko bwa ATACMS (Army Tactical Missile System) zakorewe muri Amerika
 Umuvugizi w’Inama nkuru y’igihugu ijejwe umutekano muri Amerika, John Kirby, yabwiye CNN ko ibi bisasu vyarashwe mu ntumbero yo kwerekana ko Amerika n’incuti zayo “vyama vyiteguye kwishura ku gasotoro ka Korea ya Ruguru”
 Hagati aho, igisasu ca Korea y’Epfo cagize ingorane giturika kitarashika, ariko ntavyo cononye, nk’uko igisirikare cayo kibimenyesha
 Igisirikare kivuga kandi ko misire yo mu bwoko bwa Hyunmoo-2 yari itwaye ikibombe nayo itaturitse, gica gisaba imbabazi ku bwoba cateje
 Abanyagihugu baba mu gisagara ca Gangneung kiri ku mupaka,  bavuga ko bumvise ikintu giturika baca babona umuriro mw’ijoro
 Ariko igisirikare, n’aho kivuga ko ata muntu yapfuye canke ngo akomereke, caje kwemera ibi inyuma y’amasaha indwi
 Abanyagihugu ba Gangneung bavuga ko babonye umuriro mu kirere bumva n’igiturika isaha indwi z’ijoro ryakeye mu masaha yo muri ico gihugu
 Baciye baguma mu kizime mu kiringo c’amasaha, bamwe muri bo bandika ku mbuga hwaniro babaza ivyari bibaye, berekana n’amashuho y’ivyo bari bahejeje kubona
 Videwo yerekana ikintu gisa n’icaka umuriro, kirekura n’umwotsi
 Ikinyamakuru gikorera ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi Kang Won Ilbo gisubiramwo umwe mu bakoresha izi mbuga avuga ati: "Sinshobora kuryama kuko numva ubwoba [inyuma y’aho numvise] igiturika”
 Uwundi nawe yibajije nimba yari indege igize isanganya
 Ingingo ya Pyongyang yo kurekura igisasu ca misire hejuru y’Ubuyapani ku wa kabiri yabonetse ko ari ingingo ikozwe n’ibigirankana mu ntumbero yo kwunyura ibintu, bituma Tokyo na Washington zimera magabo
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubuyapani Fumio Kishida avuga ko irungikwa ry’iki gisasu ari “inyifato y’ubukozi bw’ikibi”, mu gihe Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika, mu kiganiro yagiranye na Kishida kuri terefone, yamwemereye ko atazokwigera adohoka ku vyo Amerika yiyemeje vyo gukingira Ubuyapani
 Mu masaha y’ejo ku wa kabiri, umuvugizi wa Maison Blanche/White House John Kirby yavuze ko vyari ibintu biteye umutima uhagaze
 Mu gihe ico gisasu ca misire caca hejuru y’Ubuyapani ku wa kabiri, abanyagihugu bo mu buraruko, harimwo abo mw’izinga rya Hokkaido be n’abo mu gisagara ca Aomori, bavyuwe n’induru y’amafirimbi yo kugabisha (sirens) hamwe n’ubutumwa mu materefone yabo bwavuga ngo: "Biboneka ko Korea ya Ruguru yarekuye misire
 Murasabwe kuva mu mazu canke mwinyegeze mu kuzimu”
 Ishirahamwe ONU rirabuza Korea ya Ruguru kugerageza ibirwanisho birasa kure n’ivy’ubumara
 Kurekura za misire mu bindi bihugu canke hejuru yavyo utabigabishije canke ata kuvugana vyabanje kubaho kandi bihonyanga amabwirizwa mpuzamakungu
 Irungikwa ry’igisasu ca misire mu gaturuturu k’ejo ku wa kabiri na Korea ya Ruguru ryari rigize gatanu rikozwe na Pyongyang mu ndwi imwe gusa
 Vyinshi mu bisasu vya misire vyayo birungikwa kure cane hejuru mu kirere, ibi bigatuma bidaca mu birere vy’ibihugu bibanyi
 Ariko kukirungika hejuru y’Ubuyapani canke hafi yabwo bifasha abahinga ba Korea ya Ruguru kubigerageza nk’uko boba bari mu bihe bisanzwe vy’ikoreshwa ryavyo, nk’uko umuhinga Ankit Panda yabibwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters
 Ibi bikorwa vyatumye icuka kibi kiri hagati ya korea ya Ruguru n’Ubuyapani, icuka kiva ku bukoloni bw’Ubuyapani kuva mu 1910 gushika 1945 kuri Korea, hamwe n’inyuruzwa ry’abayapani ryakozwe na Korea ya Ruguru muri kahise
 Mu kw’icenda, Korea ya Ruguru yaremeje itegeko riyigira igihugu gitunze ibirwanisho vy’ubumara, aho n’indongozi yayo Kim Jong-un yatangaje ko n’ibiganiro bifise intumbero yo kubuza igihugu ciwe gukora no gutunga ibirwanisho vy’ubumara bidashoboka

Uburusiya bugabisha ko ingingo ya Amerika yo kurungikira Ukraine izindi mfashanyo za gisirikare “bishobora gutuma haba ugutana mu mitwe imbona nkubone” hagati y’Uburusiya  n’Uburengero
 Uwuserukira Uburusiya muri Amerika, Anatoly Antonov, avuga ko ari “ikintu kibangamiye cane” Moscou, akavuga ko Amerika “ifise uruhara mu ntambara”
 Imbere y’aha, Amerika yatangaje iyindi mfashanyo ya gisirikare ingana n’imiriyoni 625 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika igenewe Ukraine
 Ibirwanisho rutura vya Amerika bivugwa ko ari vyo vyatumye Ukraine igira inguvu nyinshi gusumba ingabo z’Uburusiya zigaruriye ubutaka bw’ico gihugu
 Muri zino ndwi za vuba, ingabo za Ukraine ziriko zitera intambwe mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko no mu bumanuko bw’igihugu
 Mu bikoresho vyemewe na Amerika ubu harimwo za nkoho ntahusha zine zo mu bwoko bwa Himars zirekura ibisasu vya muzinga vyinshi ica rimwe
 Vyose hamwe, Washington imaze guha Kyiv imfashanyo ya gisirikare ingana n’imiriyaridi 17 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika kuva Perezida Vladimir Putin  w’Uburusiya ateye Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma
 Mw’itangazo ryo ku wa kane w’indwi iheze, Antonov yagabishije ko ingendo ya Amerika yo “kubandanya isukira ibirwanisho rutura muri Ukraine ata kindi bivamwo atari uko Washington ica iboneka ko iri muri ino ntambara”
 Yavuze ko ibi bishobora gutuma “amaraso abandanya aseseka igihe kirekire abandi bantu bakahasiga ubuzima”
 Uyu muserukizi w’Uburusiya avuga ati: "Dusavye Amerika guhagarika ibikorwa vyayo vy’agasotoro bishobora gutuma haba ingaruka mbi zikomeye”
 Inyuma yo gutakaza bikomeye ku rugamba muri Ukraine, Uburusiya bumenyesha ko buzokwivuna bukoresheje uburyo bwose buhari – n’ibirwansiho vy’ubumara bidashizwe inyuma
 Uburusiya burabandanya kandi n’umugambi wabwo wo kugerageza kwihagira intara zine za Ukraine: Donetsk na Luhansk mu buseruko, hamwe na Kherson na Zaporizhzhia mu bumanuko
 Hagati aho, muri zino ntara zose, Uburusiya nta n’imwe bugenzura yose, mu gihe ingabo za Ukraine zibandanya zisatira ku muvuduko munini muri  ino misi
 Aya majambo ya Antonov yo kugabisha aje inyuma y’akanya gato Perezida Joe Biden n’icegera ciwe Kamala Harris bavuganye ibijanye n’iyindi mfashanyo boha Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky  wa Ukraine
 Mw’intangazo, ibiro vya prezida wa Amerika, Maison Blanche/White House, bishimangira ko "Amerika itazokwigera yemera ingingo y’Uburusiya yo kwihagira ubutaka bwa Ukraine
 "Perezida Biden yariyemeje kubandanya ashigikira Ukraine mu ntambara yayo yo kwivuna igitero c’Uburusiya mu gihe cose izomara”
 Iri tangazo rivuga ko mu mfashanyo nshasha ya gisirikare harimwo za nkoho za rutura "Himars, hamwe n’amamodokari ntamenwa”
 Ibi bikoho rutura vya muzinga vyakorewe muri Amerika birakoreshwa mu gutera ibirindiro vy’ingabo z’Uburusiya, nk’ibigo bitegurirwamwo intambara, hamwe n’ububiko bw’amasasu
 Birakoreshwa kandi mu gutera ibiraro, harimwo n’ivyegereye intara ya Kherson iri mu minwe y’Uburusiya, Ukraine iriko igerageza kwisubiza

