Umukuru wa Tchétchénie/Chechnya Ramzan Kadyrov avuga ko abahungu biwe batatu b’imyaka 14, 15 na 16, bagiye vuba kurungikwa ku rugamba muri Ukraine gufasha ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Kadyrov ni incuti pfa mpfe ya Vladimir Putin, n’aho aherutse kunegura abarongoye igisirikare c’Uburusiya
 Aciye ku mbuga hwaniro, yanditse ko umugabo ategerezwa kwigisha abahungu biwe gukingira umuryango, abanyagihugu n’igihugu cabavyaye
 Uburusiya bwarateye igikumu ku masezerano ya ONU  afise intumbero yo gukingira abana bari musi y’imyaka 18  kugira ntibakoreshee mu ntambara
 Sentare mpuzamakungu mpanavyaha ifata ko gukoresha mu ntambara abana bari musi y’imyaka 18 ari icaha co mu ntambara
 Ariko Uburusiya ntibwemera iyi sentare
 Mu butumwa burebure yacishije ku rubuga rwa Telegram, Kadyrov yavuze ko abahungu biwe batanguye guhabwa inyigisho za gisirikare bakiri bato cane, ko rero igihe kigeze ko barungikwa mu ntambara nyezina
 Yifatiye kandi mu gahanga abantu b’“ibijambojambo” bavuga ko incuti z’uyu mukuru wa Tchétchénie  zitarungitswe mu gikorwa ca gisirikare muri Ukraine
 Ubu butumwa bwaherekejwe na videwo yahinguwe neza yerekana abahungu biwe bariko bararasa inkoho zitandukanye mu myimenyerezo
 Hari bamwe bashinyaguriza ingabo za Tchétchénie muri Ukraine kubera ko baboneka bitayeho cane gukwiragiza ku mbuga hwaniro amavidewo ataco amaze aho gufata inkoho bakarwana
 Kadyrov arongoye iyi Repubulika yegukira Uburusiya kuva mu 2007, igihe Vladimir Putin amugena kurongora aka karere ko mu bumanuko
 Kuva ico gihe muri Tchétchénie ni agahengwe, inyuma y’imyaka ishika cumi yamaze mu ntambara irondera kwikukira, ariko ikananirwa
 Ariko  Kadyrov aranegurwa ko atwaza umukazo, kandi ko yigira sindabibazwa mu gihe agateka ka zina muntu kariko karahonyangwa
 Kadyrov arashigikiye cane Vladimir Putin, kandi ingabo za Tchétchénie ziri ku rugamba muri Ukraine kuva intambara itangura
 Hagati aho, inyuma y’aho igisirikare c’Uburusiya gitakarije uturere mu ntara za Kharkiv na Donetsk, yaraneguye abarongoye igisirikare c’Uburusiya, aho yifatiye mu gahanga intwazangabo imwe ko “ataco imaze” anavuga kandi ko n’uburyo shingiro bukenye
 Yateye akamo kandi Uburusiya gufatira Ukraine izindi ngingo zikaze, harimwo gukoresha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara bito bito
 Kremlin yishuye ko ingingo nk’izi zidashobora gufatwa ku bishobisho
 Kadyrov yashikirije aya majambo yo kunegura inyuma y’aho ingabo z’Uburusiya zivaniwe mu gisagara ca Lyman mu ntara ya Donetsk iri mu buseruko bwa Ukraine – urwabaye uruhombo rukomeye kuri Moscou
 Ifatwa ry’iki gisagara ryabaye intambwe ikomeye ku ngabo za Ukraine kubera gishobora gukoreshwa nk’inzira yo gushika mu tundi turere twa Ukraine twigaruriwe n’Uburusiya
 Cakoreshwa n’Uburusiya nk’ikirindiro co gushikizamwo uburyo mu rugamba rwabwo
 Ugutsindwa muri Lyman cabaye ikintu gikomeye, kuko vyabaye umusi umwe gusa habaye ibirori i Moscou vyo gutera igikumu ku masezerano yo kwihagira izi ntara zine za Ukraine – harimwo na Donetsk, aho Lyman isanzwe iri
 Intara za Donetsk, Luhansk, Zaporizhzhia na Kherson zose zarakoze icitwa amatora ya kamarampaka yo kwegukira Uburusiya mu kwezi guheze, amatora yafashwe na Ukraine n’incuti zayo z’Uburengero nk’ “amanyanga”
 Ku mugoroba wo ku wa Mungu, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky yavuze ko ingabo za Ukraine zari zigaruriye kandi uturere tumwe tumwe mu ntara ya Kherson
 Umukuru w’iyi ntara yashizweho n’Uburusiya, Vladimir Saldo, yavuze ko ibintu muri ako karere bitari vyoroshe, yongera avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zateye intambwe
 Muri izi ntara zine ziherutse kwihagirwa n’Uburusiya, nta n’imwe bugenzura yose, ibi bigatuma abantu bibaza ingene bizogenda – cane cane mu bice bigenzurwa na Ukraine
 Kremlin ivuga ko izobaza abanyagihugu b’intara za Zaporizhzhia na Kherson ku bijanye n’aho imbibe zoca, iki kikerekana ko Uburusiya bushobora kwihoza ivyo kuvuga ko bwiyeguriye izi ntara zose uko ziri
 Ibintu biratandukanye muri Luhansk na Donetsk
 Imbere gato y’uko intambara itangura, Putin yaremeje ko izo ntara uko zakabaye zibaye Repubulika zigenga, ariko ubu – nk’uko Moscou ibibona – zatoye zikemeza ko zegukiye Uburusiya

By Hugh Schofield BBC News, Paris Niba Ubufaransa bushaka kuba indongozi  imbere y'ibindi bihugu vya Buraya muri iki kiringo gishasha co kwigwanako mu vya gisirikare, bigenda gute ngo intererano yabwo mu twigoro tw'intambara muri Ukarine ibe ari nto cane? Ico ni  ikibazo kitaryoshe kwishura cibazwa na bamwe mu bahinga b'imikenyuro muri ico  gihugu, aho bariko barasunika prezida Emmanuel Macron ngo afate ingingo yo kwongereza  ibigwanisho aha Ukraine
 Isuzuma ku rubuga muri Pologne/Poland na Ukraine ryasanze intererano y’Ubufaransa mu bigwanisho biva hanze birungikwa muri Ukraine idashika na 2%, kure cane ya Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika itanga 49%, ariko kandi inyuma ya Pologne (22%) , n'Ubudagi (9%)
 François Heisbourg, ashobora kuba ari mu bahinga bumvirizwa cane mu bihweza ibijanye no kwivuna agira ati: “Nari mfise inpungenge ku kwizigira ibiharuro vyerekana Ubufaransa hasi cane ku rutonde rw’ibihugu biterera”
 “Niho naca ngenda aho intererano ishikira muri Pologne   kuraba ibitangwa ingene bingana, ntaravye ibiba vyemewe
 “Ariko ibihaururo vyaciye bivanaho impungenge nari mfise
 Ubufaransa buri kure cane hasi kuri urwo rutonde -buza ubugira icenda
” Inyishu y’abategetsi i Paris yabaye: “Ego, ariko


” Ego, ibiharuro vyerekeye imfashanyo ntibibesha, ariko hari ibindi vyo gufatirako
 Ubwa mbere, abategetsi bajejwe ivyo kwivuna abansi bavuga ko igipimo nyaco c’imfashanyo ya gisirikare ari ubwiza bw’igitanzwe kurusha ubwinshi
 Hari ibihugu bitanga ibirundo vy’ibigwanisho vyataye igihe
 Ubufaransa bwatanze ibikoho 18 vyo mu bwoko bwa Caesar birasa vya muzinga, ivyo bikaba biri mu vyo abanya-Ukraine bavuga ko biriko birabafasha cane ku rugamba
 Bongerako kandi ko, Ubufaransa co kimwe n’ibindi bihugu vy’iburengrazuba, bwagabanuye kurundarunda ibigwanisho kuva intambara yo kurabana ay'ingwe irangiye
 Ama Ceasar Ubufaransa bwahaye Ukraine angana n’ica kane ca bene ivyo bigwanisho Ubufaransa buja buravana aha bujana hariya
 Ntibushobora gutanga ibisumba aho butishize mu ngorane  mu bindi bice vy’isi aho bufise uruhara nko muri Sahel na Indo-Pacific
 Gen Jérome Pellistrandi w’ikinyamakuru mu bijanye na gisirikare ati: “Dusa n’abari inyuma y’ibindi bihugu, ariko Ubufaransa bufise ugushaka kwo kugira uruhara ruboneka
” Izo nsiguro  si izo gufata minenerwe, nk’uko bivugwa na Heisbourg
 Ikibazo n’uko kutaba ugaragara cane aho bikenewe, Ubufaransa buzohava busanga bwikuye bwonyene mu bo kwerekezako amaso
 “Igihe nari Kyiv, abantu bose bari bafise urupfasoni
 Sinari nzi ko abanya-Ukraine babona ko ataco tubafasha
 “Ubiravye  vyari bibi kurusha aho
 Jewe nabonye umenga turiko turaba nk’abataco bamaze
” Heisbourg avuga ko igikurikira coroshe
 Ukraine izovugana n’ibihugu izi ko bishobora kuyiha ibigwanisho ikeneye
 Ubufaransa muri iki gihe ntiburi muri ivyo
 Ariko hari ikindi kibangamye ku Bufaransa
 Kuba Ubufaransa busa n’ubutagaragara muri Ukraine bibangamira intumbero yabwo yo kuba indongozi mu kibazo c’ukwivuna abansi i Buraya
 Hari ibihugu muri Buraya y’Ubuseruko bifise impungenge kuri prezida Macron, vyibaza ko  mu mezi ya mbere y’intambara yafashe umurongo woroshe cane ku mukuru w’Uburusiya Vladimir Putin
 Ubu hari abasigaye bavuga  ko Ubufaransa n’ubu bugifise udutima tubiri ku bijanye n’uko Ukraine yotsinda iyo ntambara
 Kuri Pierre Haroche,  atanga ivyigwa ku mutekano mpuzamakungu kuri kaminuza Queen Mary University of London, kuvuga ivyo ni ukurenganya Ubufaransa -kandi sico gituma urugero ruto rw’ibigwanisho bihabwa Ukraine
 Ariko arahuza cane n’abavuga ko  Ubufaransa bukeneye kwongereza intererano yabwo vuba hashoboka, kugira buhumurize ibuhugu vya Buraya y’Ubuseruko nka Pologne “ko turi ku murongo umwe”
 Avuga ati: “Ihangiro ry’Ubufaransa ko Uburaya bwokwikwiza ku bijanye no kwivuna rishingiye ku gukomeza inganda z’ibigwanisho biciye mu gushira uburyo hamwe mu kurondera ibikoresho
 “Ariko ukeneye ko haba ugushira uburyo hamwe, utegerezwa kwereka ibindi bihugu ko ufise iyo ntumbero nyene ku vyerekeye umutekano wacu”
 Dr Haroche  ahamagarira Ubufaransa kurungika ibiduga  vy’intambara 50 vyo mu bwoko bwa Leclerc
 Heisbourg we yoshima ko harungikwa ibikoresho vyo mu kirere avuga ko Ukraine ikeneye kurusha ibindi
 Dr Haroche avuga   ati: “Ni nka kizimyamwoto
 “Iyo hadutse umuriro mu nzu y’umubanyi, ni vyiza gusumba guca wihuta kumurungikira kizimyamwoto yawe , hanyuma nturindire ko umuriro ubanza gutandukira inzu yawe"

Natasha Booty B﻿BC News Umukuru mushasha wa Burkina Faso  , Capt Ibrahim Traoré, yasavye abashikiranganji “gukora bihuta” kugira batore inyishu z’ibibazo “vyihuta” bihanze igihugu birimwo umutekano muke uterwa n’abagwana biyitirira idini rya Islam (islamists)
 Umugabo yatembagaje ku wa gatanu yemeye kuva ku butegetsi nk’uko abarongozi b’amadini babivuze
 Bavuze ko  Capt Traoré yemeye ugutanga imihoho(ukwegura)  kwa  Lt Col Paul-Henri Damiba hamwe n’ivyo yasavye
 Yagiye muri Togo, nk’uko bivugwa n’umuvugizi wa reta y’ico gihugu
 Mu majwi yahanahanywe cane ku mbuga hwaniro, Lt Col Paul-Henri Damiba yavuze ko yifurije umutegetsi mushasha wa Burkina Faso kuroranirwa muri vyose
 Ntibiramenyekana niba yari wenyene igihe ayo majwi yafatwa
 Ku wa mungu, Capt Traoré yavuze ko iguhugu gihanzwe n’ibibazo vyihuta mu bisata  vyose, ”kuva ku mutekano gushika ku kwivuna abansi, amagara y’abantu, ibikorwa vy’imibereho y’abantu,  gushika ku bikorwa remezo”, ko rero hari hageze ko reta ”iheba inzira nende zo mu biro zidakenewe”
 Ashaka inyishu zihuta ku bibazo bikomeye, ico bamwe babona nko gushaka kwerekeza ku Burusiya
 Ubufaransa n’Uburusiya biri mu rugamba rwo kurushanya kugira ijambo mu bihugu vyinshi vyahoze bitwawe gikoroni n’Ubufaransa muri Afrika y’uburengero n’iyo hagati
 Mu mpera z’indwi, ibibanza vy’inyungu z’Ubufaransa vyaratewe, inyuma y’aho bivugiwe ko Lt Col Damiba yahungiye mw’ikambi ya gisirikare y’Ubufaransa ku murwa mukuru, Ouagadougou
 Ubufaransa bwavuze ko ico cari igikorwa c’abantu batabwerekwa bari mu myiyerekano ‘bahenzwe n’isekeza ry’amakuru atariyo ryo kuturwanya’
 Bamwe muri Ouagadougou  baririmvye ivyivugo bishigikira Uburusiya bazungagiza n’amabendera y’Uburusiya igihe bariko bararamutsa umutegetsi wa gisirikare mushasha n’urukurikirane rwiwe ku wa mungu
 Abona Ubufaransa nk’ubushigikiye uwo yatembagaje, kandi yamenyesheje ko yiteguriye gukorana n’impande nshasha mu guhangana n’ikibazo c’abagarariji bitwaza idini rya Islam, ivyo abaraba ibintu n’ibindi babona ko vyoba bisigura guha akazi abacangero b’abarusiya
 Bene abo bacangero ba gisirikare bivugwa  basanzwe bariko barakora mu gihugu kibanyi ca Mali inyuma y’aho ingabo z’Ubufaransa ziviriyeyo bitumwe n’ukutumvikana hagati y’Ubufaransa n’abategetsi ba gisirikare ba Mali
 Abo barusiya bagirizwa gukora amahano no kwica abanyagihugu  basanzwe, ivyo Uburusiya bwagumye buhakana
 Umukuru w’iyo kompanyi y’abo bacangero b’abarusiya Wagner, Yevgeny Prigozhin, yarashimye ko zahinduye imirisho muri Burkina Faso
 Hagati aho reta y’Uburusiya yavuze ku wa mbere ko “yifuza ko ibintu muri Burkina Faso vyosubira kuba ibisanzwe vuba hashoboka”
 Burkina Faso igenzura ibice 60% gusa vy’igihugu, nk’uko abahinga babivuga, mu gihe intureka y’abagwana biyitirira idini rya Islam iguma irushiriza gukomera
 Ishirahamwe ry’Ubumwe bwa Afrika ryasavye ko ubutegetsi bwosubira kugengwa n’ibwirizwa shingiro bitarenze mu kwezi kw’indwi mu 2023, aho rikaba rihahuriza n’ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika y’uburengero (ECOWAS/CEDEAO)  ko ikurwa rya  Lt Col Damiba riteye kubiri n’ibwirizwa shingiro
 Ariko mu nyuma CEDEAO yakeje impande zose muri Burkina Faso kuba zarumvikanye kugira ibibazo  bitorerwe inyishu mu mahoro” kuko iminsi yo kugwanira ubutegetsi yarangiye ata maraso asesetse
 Lt Col Damiba ku wa mungu yaratanze imihoho nawe ubutegetsi  bushasha bumwemerera kwubahiriza ibintu indwi – harimwo gukingira umutekano wiwe n’uw’umuryango wiwe, umwumvikano w’uko habandanywa umugambi wo kunywanisha abanya-Burkina Faso hamwe no kwubahiriza kwiyemeza gusubiza ubutegetsi mu minwe y’abanyagihugu basanzwe (civil) mu kiringo c’imyaka ibiri
 Uwo mu colonel nawe yari yatembagaje prezida Roch Kaboré mu kwezi kwa Nzero (1), avuga ko yananiwe no gutora inyishu z’ikibazo c’umutekano
 Benshi muri Burkina Faso bamaze igihe ata mutekano bumva bafise
 Ubugarariji bw’abitwaza idini rya Islam bwadutse mu 2015, hapfa ibihumbi  abandi bagereranywa muri miriyoni zibiri barata ingo zabo
 Ibaye coup d’etat igira icenda muri Burkina Faso kuva ico gihugu cikukiye ku Bufaransa mu 1960

Abantu n’imuburiburi 174 nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko bapfiriye mu musunikano wadutse igihe hariko haba urukino rw’umupira w’amaguru, rimwe mu masanganya mabi cane kw’isi amaze kubera mu kibuga
 Ababa 180 barakomerekeye muri uwo musunikano inyuma y’aho umurwi Arema FC utsindiwe muhira  2-3  n’umurwi w’abakeba ruhebwa wa Persebaya Surabaya muri ico kibuga cari carengeje  abantu mu karere ka Malanga, intara ya East Java
 Ibi vyabaye igihe abapolisi batera ivyuka bikoroza amosozi abafana bari binjiye mu kibuga ku mugoroba  w’ejo ku wa gatandatu
 Umwe mu mabibonye, yitwa Dwi, yabwiye ikinyamakuru Kompas co muri Indonesia gikorera ku rubugua ngurukanabumenyi  ko yabonye “abantu benshi bahonyanzwe” bariko bagerageza guhunga
 Umushikiranganji ajejwe umutekano muri ico gihugu avuga ko ico kibuga, ku bantu bangana na 38
000 categerezwa kwakira carengejeko 4000
 Perezida Joko Widodo yategetse ko inkino zose zitegekanijwe mw’ihiganwa ryo mu cicaro ca mbere muri Indonesia zihagarara gushika amatohoza arangiye
 Ishirahamwe ry’umupira w’amaguru kw’isi, FIFA, rivuga ko “ata vyuka” bikwiye kwinjizwa canke gukoreshwa n’abazamu canke abapolisi mu gihe c’inkino
