Serhiy Cherevatyi, umuvugizi w’ingabo za Ukraine mu buseruko, avuga ko umurwi munini w’ingabo z’Uburusiya i Lyman "wagoswe" kandi n’uturere turi mu micungararo  y’iki gisagara ko twabohojwe
 Yabwiye imboneshakure yo muri Ukraine ati “ibiharuro dufise bitwereka ko ingabo z’Uburusiya ziri hagati ya 5000 na 5500 zari i Lyman”, ariko ko iki gitigiri ubu cagabanutse kubera “intambara ziheruka” aho abasirikare b’Uburusiya “benshi” bishwe canke barakomereka
 Cherevatyi avuga ko amayeri yose ingabo z’Uburusiya zakoresheje kugira zirabe ingene zokwigobotora “yanse”
 Avuga kandi ko mu gihe Lyman yoramuka ibohojwe n’ingabo za Ukraine yozifasha gutera zisatira Kreminna na Severodonetsk, vyompi bikaba ari ibirindiro kirumara ku ngabo z’abarusiya
 "Ni ikintu kandi gikomeye cane mu bikorwa vyacu kuko  - nk’uko Perezida Zelensky yabivuze ejo – ingabo za Ukraine ziratanguye gutegeko uko zishaka ko ibintu bimera – ntabwo ari ukwivuna gusa”
 Aheraheza avuga ko igikorwa ca gisirikare kitararangira
 Ibintu bigenda bihinduka ku muvuduko udasanzwe mu micungararo ya Lyman mu ntara ya Donetsk iri mu buseruko
 Hasohotse videwo isa n’iyerekana abasirikare ba Ukraine baduza ibendera rya Ukraine kw’irembo ry’iki gisagara, aho ibihumbi vy’ingabo z’Uburusiya zivugwa ko zugaraniwe
 Muri iyi videwo – yerekanywe n’umukuru w’ibiro vya Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky, Andriy Yermak – abasirikare babiri bumvikana bavuga mu rurimi rw’ikinya-Ukraine ngo: "[Uno musi] igenekerezo rya 1 Gitugutu
 Turazinguruye ibendera ry’igihugu cacu turishize ku butaka bwacu
 "Lyman
 Yose izoba iya Ukraine", niko bavuga, bashimira imirwi y’abarwanyi ba Ukraine
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya muri aka karere zasavye abazirongoye ko zova muri ico gisagara – ariko aka kamo kamiriwe kure, nk’uko umutegetsi wo hejuru wa Ukraine abivuga
 Umukuru w’intara ya Luhansk Serhiy Haidai avuga ko ubu ingabo z’Uburusiya zisigaranye inzira zibiri gusa: Kugerageza kwicira inzira canke kwishikana
 Haidai yongerako y’uko amayira hafi yose yo guhunga canke kubashikanira vya nkenerwa nk’amasasu i Lyman ubu adahita
 Hagati aho, ibi avuga ntibirashobora guhinyuzwa
 Ejo ku wa gatanu Denis Pushilin, umukuru w’intara ya Donetsk  yashizweho n’Uburusiya, yavuze ko  Lyman yari "yakikujwe igice " kandi ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zariko zirwanako “n’inguvu zazo zose zisigaranye”
 Kuva bwigaruriye Lyman mu mpera z’ukwa gatanu, ingabo z’Uburusiya zahinduye iki gisagara kiri mu ntara ya Donetsk nk’ikirindiro gikomeye kizoshikiramwo ingabo zirungikwa ku rugamba hamwe n’ibikoresho vya gisirikare
 Iki gisagara kandi ni igituro gikomeye c’ibarabara ry’indarayi, rifatanya intara za Donetsk, Luhansk na Kharkiv mu buseruko no mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya zababa 5000 zishobora kuba muri uno mwanya zugaraniwe i Lyman,  kandi mu gihe Ukraine yoyibohoza rwoba ari urundi ruhombo rukomeye rwa gisirikare ku Burusiya kuva iyi ntambara itanguye ku wa 24 z’ukwa kabiri
 Vyofasha kandi ingabo za Ukraine gukubura burundu igice c’uburaruko bw’intara ya Donetsk no gutera zisugereza intara ya Luhansk bihana urubibe
 Ukraine ivuga ko ingabo zayo zamaze kwigarurira ibigwati bibiri biri mu micungararo ya Lyman
 Mu cegeranyo c’igendereza bwama butanga ku bijanye n’ingene ibintu bimeze muri Ukraine, ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Ubwongereza buvuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya “ata gukekeranya cane” zateye imodoka z’ubutabazi ejo – mu gitero Ukraine ivuga ko ciciwemwo abantu n’imiburiburi 30 bari mu modoka za gisivire
 Igisasu cakoreshejwe muri ico gitero cari “igisasu ca misire co gukingira ikirere kandi kirasa kure, kikaba cakoreshejwe mu bitero vyo hasi”, nk’uko itangazo ry’ubu bushikiranganji ribivuga
 Ryongerako y’uko ububiko bw’Uburusiya bw’ibisasu vyo muri ubu bwoko ari buto, ko rero ari ukubikoresha iyo bikenewe, mu gukorora indege canke za misire, hako bikoreshwa mu ntambara yo hasi
 Ubu bushikiranganji buvuga ko ikoreshwa ry’ibi bisasu ku mu ntambara yo hasi vyerekana ko amasasu ariko arahera, cane cane za misire zidahusha zirasa kure
 Iki gitero cabaye mu ntara ya Zaporizhzhia iherutse gutangazwa na Vladimir Putin ko ari igice c’ubutaka bw’Uburusiya, aho hri ejo

Perezida Joe Biden agabisha Uburusiya ko Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zitazokangwa n’iterabwoba ataco rimaze inyuma y’aho Vladimir Putin yihagiye intara zine yigaruriye muri Ukraine
 Putin aboneka ko akangisha gukoresha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara mu ntumbero yo gukingira uturere yigaruriye
 Yaraye atangaje ko kuva ubu utu turere ari ubutaka bw’Uburusiya
 Umunyamabanga wa OTAN/NATO Jens Stoltenberg avuga ko ukwigarurira utu turere ari “ukwunyura ibintu ku rugero rutari bwigere rubaho kuva iyi ntambara itanguye”
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije, umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yatangaje ko abanyagihugu ba Kherson, Zaporizhzhia, Luhansk na Donetsk batoye bakemeza ko baja “hamwe n’abantu babo, igihugu cabo”
 Aha yariko avuga ico yise amatora ya kamarampaka aheruka muri utwo turere, ariko Ukraine n’ibihugu vy’uburengero bikaba vyiyamiriza aya matora vyita ko ari amanyanga
 Ariko ahanini Putin yakoresheje ijambo ryiwe mu kwifatira mu gahanga Uburengero
 Yavuze ko Amerika ari yo “ntandaro ya vyose” mu gukoresha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara ku Buyapani mu mpera z’intambara ya kabiri y’isi yose, igisa c’icateye ubwoba isi yose
 Mu ndwi iheze, Putin yavuze ko igihugu ciwe “igifise ibirwanisho bitandukanye vyo gutikiza inganda” kandi ko azokoresha “uburyo bwose dufise”, yongera ko ati “si ndiko ndayayata”
 Kremlin iratomora neza ko igitero ico ari co cose ku turere dushasha iherutse kwihagira kizofatwa nk’igitero ku butaka bw’Uburusiya, ibishobora gutuma ibintu vyunyuka muri ino ntambara
 Perezida Biden ariyamiriza “amajambo n’iterabwoba vy’umunyagwangara” ashikirizwa na mugenziwe w’Uburusiya, ariko akongerako y’uko Putin adashobora kubakanga
 Perezida Biden ati: "Amerika n’incuti zayo ntibashobora gukangwa”
 Yaciye abwira umukuru w’igihugu w’Uburusiya amuhanga, mu gutuma urutoke muri kamera
 "Amerika iriteguye neza, iri kumwe n’incuti zayo za OTAN gukingira n'insentimetero imwe gusa y'ubutaka bwa OTAN”, niko avuga, ashaka kuvuga rwa rurani rw’ukwivunira umwansi hamwe ruhuza ibihugu vy’uburengero
 "Putin, ntuhave utahura nabi ivyo ndiko ndavuga: n'isentimetero imwe gusa"
 Inyuma y’aho gato, umutegetsi mukuru mu vyo umutekano mu butegetsi bwa Biden yavuze ko n’aho hariho igihamana kibi ko Moscou ishobora kwikora ku birwanisho vy’ubumara, biboneka ko atari ivy’ubu
 Ukraine yaciye itanguza urundi rugamba, ku muvuduko munini, rwo kwinjira muri OTAN, ubwo nyene inyuma y’ijambo rya Putin
 Perezida  Volodymyr Zelensky avuga ko mu bisanzwe Ukraine yamye ari umunywanyi w’iri shirahamwe ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe, anagiriza Moscou ko iriko irasambura imbibe “ikoresheje ubwicanyi, gutyoza, gufata nabi abantu n’ibinyoma"
 Stoltenberg wa OTAN ariko yirinze kugwa mu mutego, mu kuvuga ko ingingo izofatwa n’ibihugu 30 vyene iri shirahamwe
 Abanywanyi b’uru runani “ntibemera kandi ntibarota bemera” ko agace ako ari ko kose kavuye kuri Ukraine ari akarere k’Uburusiya, nk’uko Stoltenberg yabibwiye abanyamakuru, aca yagiriza Putin ko “ariko arakangisha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara atiyumviriye”
 Avuga ko ukwihagira utu turere ari “igihe gikomeye” muri ino ntambara
 Umukuru w’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya Ursula von der Leyen avuga ko "ingingo iteye kubiri n’amategeko yo kwihagira ubutaka bwa Ukraine yatangajwe na Putin nta na kimwe izohindura”
 "Uturere twose twihagiwe n’Abarusiya bateye igihugu ni ubutaka bwa Ukraine kandi tuzoguma twegukira iki gihugu cigenga”
 Mu gihe Putin yariko arashikiriza ijambo, ku birometero 750 uja mu bumanuko, ingabo ziwe zariko zirakikuzwa n’ingabo za Ukraine mu gisagara ca Lyman, igisagara ngirakamaro mu ntara ya Donetsk iri mu buseruko – kamwe mu turere twihagiwe n’Uburusiya
 Igisirikare ca Ukraine cagumye kinyegeza amakuru y’ingene ingabo zayo ziriko zirasatira muri ako karere, ariko videwo imwe yakwiragijwe ku mbuga hwaniro isa n’iyerekana ingabo za Kyiv ziri hagati mu gisagara ca Yampil kiri ku birometero 16 gusa mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Lyman
 Ni mu gihe mu masaha yitereye ya nijoro ku wa gatanu umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi yatangaje ko ingabo z’igihugu ciwe zigaruriye ikigwati ca Drobysheve kiri ku birometero umunani mu buraruko bushira uburengero bwa Lyman
 Mu vyabereye ahandi, abanyagihugu bababa 30 mu ntara ya Zaporizhzhia  barishwe mu gitero ca roketi ku mamodoka ya gisivire
 Ico gihe nyene, Uburusiya bwatesheje icemezo c’inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano cari kwiyamiriza ingingo yabwo yo kwihagira uturere tune bwigaruriye
 Umuserukizi wa Moscou, Vasily Nebenzia, yavuze ko ari ibintu bitabaho kurondera kwagiriza igihugu ntayegayezwa muri iyo nama
 Mu gihe Kremlin yaburizamwo iki cemezo, Ubuhindi n’Ubushinwa vyovyo vyahisemwo kutagira aho bihagaze

Umukapiteni mu gisirikare ca Burkina Faso yatangaje  ku mboneshakure y’igihugu ko yabogoje indongozi y’igihugu, Liyetena-Koloneli (Lt Col ) Paul-Henri Damiba
 Ibrahim Traore avuga ko yatembagaje intwaro ya  Lt Col Damiba kubera adashoboye kurwanya inyeshamba ziyitirira idini rya Islam
 Atangaza kandi ko imbibe z’igihugu zugaye mu gihe kitazwi kandi ko ibikorwa vyose vya poritike bibaye birahagarikwa
 Mu kwa mbere, akarwi k’abasirikare kari karongowe na Lt Col Damiba katembagaje reta yari yitorewe n’abanyagihugu, kavuga ko yananiwe no gutuza ibitero vy’izo nyeshamba
 Ariko reta yiwe nayo nyene ntiyashoboye kurwanya imigumuko iterwa n’izi nyeshamba ziyitirira idini rya Islam
 Ku wa mbere, abasirikare 11 barishwe igihe bari baherekeje imodoka za gisivire mu buraruko bw’igihugu
 Mu gatondo k’ejo ku wa gatanu, Lt Col Damiba yasavye abanyagihugu kuguma batekanye inyuma y’aho humvikaniye inkoho zikomakomeye mu bice vy’umugwa mukuru
 Abasirikare barenga 20  - benshi muri bo bambaye ibitambara bibapfuka mu maso – bagiye kuboneka ku mboneshakure imbere gato y’isaha zibiri z’ijoro mu masaha y’ico gihugu
 Itangazo ryateweko igikumu na Traore  rivuga riti: "Mu gihe ibintu vyabadanya vyunyuka, twaragerageje incuro nyinshi kwumvisha  Damiba ko yotunganya gushasha intwaro yiwe ikitaho gusumba ikibazo c’umutekano
 "Ibikorwa vya Damiba vyagiye bitwereka ko intumbero ziwe zari ziteye kubiri n’ivyo twumvikanye
 Uno musi twafashe ingingo yo kubogoza Damiba”
 Hatangajwe kandi amasaha ya guma mu rugo yo kuva isaha zitatu z’ijoro gushika isaha cumi n’imwe z’agatondo
 Nta wuzi aho Lt Col Damiba aherereye
 Amerika ivuga ko itewe amakenga cane n’ibibera muri Burkina Faso igasaba abayo kwirinda ingendo zo hagati mu gihugu
 Umuvugizi w’umunyamabanga wa reta avuga ati: "Dusaba ko ituze rigaruka ababifisemwo uruhara nabo bakigumya”
 Ishirahamwe ry’ubutunzi rihuza ibihugu vya Afrika y’uburengero CEDEAO/ECOWAS  ririyamiriza iri tembagazwa ry’ubutegetsi, rikavuga ko “rishimangiye ryivuye inyuma ko ridashigikiye na gato ugushikira canke ugushaka kugumana ubutegetsi mu nzira iteye kubiri n’ibwirizwashingiro”
 Mu bucagucagu bw’ejo ku wa gatanu, amabombe n’amasasu vyarasiranye ku mugwa mukuru, Ouagadougou, bimwe biva hafi y’ikirimba c’umukuru w’igihugu no mu makambi makuru makuru
 Imbere y’uko izuba riseruka, iki gisagara mu bisanzwe kiba cuzuye abantu casa n’icera, abasirikare bazibira  amabarabara, bacungereye n’ibibanza bikuru bikuru
 Imboneshakure y’igihugu yarahagaritse ibiganiro vyayo, inkoho zikaba zabandanije zumvikana umusi wose
 Lt Col Damiba yavuga ko hari “ibintu bidatomoye” bitewe “agashavu” kari mu basirikare bamwe bamwe, mu gihe ibihuha vy’itembagazwa ry’ubutegetsi vyaguma vyiyongera
 Mu gihe yasaba abanyagihugu kuguma batekanye bakirinda gukokeza baciye ku mbuga hwaniro, uyu mutegetsi wa gisirikare yavuga ko “hari ibiganiro vyariko biraba mu ntumbero yo kugarukana ituze”
 Mu kwa mbere, Lt Col Damiba yatembagaje Perezida Roch Kaboré, avuga ko yari yananiwe no kurwanya imigumuko y’inyeshamba ziyitirira Islam
 Igihe ashikirizwa ubutegetsi mu kwa kabiri, akarwi k’abasirikare kasenyuye ubutegetsi kavuze kati: “Dufise ibikoresho vyose bisabwa kugira dutsinde iyi ntambara”
 Ariko abanyagihugu ntibacizeye umutekano mbere muri ino ndwi habaye imyiyerekano mu turere dutandukanye tw’igihugu
 Ku muhingamo w’ejo ku wa gatanu, bamwe mu bari mu myiyerekano barihaye amabarabara yo ku mugwa mukuru basaba ko Lt Col Damiba yirukanwa ku butegetsi
 Imigumuko y’abiyitirira idini rya Islam yadutse mu 2015 muri Burkina Faso, ihitana ibihumbi n’ibihumbi bishwe abandi nabo baharurwa mu miriyoni zibiri bata izabo
 Kuva iki gihugu cikukira mu 1960, iki gihugu kimaze kubamwo ama coups d’Etat umunani

Abanyabulaya icenda bahagaritswe mu myiyerekano yo muri Irani yandurutse ku mugore yapfiriye mu gasho, ikaba imaze guhitana abatari bake
 Abajejwe igendereza bahagaritse abantu bikekwa ko ari “abakozi b’ibigo vyo mu mahanga bijejwe igendereza” bamwe bari mu myiyerekano nyene, abandi nabo bagakorera binyegeje, nk’uko ibinyamakuru vy’ico gihugu bibivuga
 Iyi migumuko nta kintu na kimwe cerekana ko yimirije guhagarara, mu gihe abapfa babandanya biyongera
 Iyi migumuko yadutse ku mugwa mukuru Tehran ica ikwira igihugu cose inyuma y’aho umugore w’umu-kurde, Mahsa Amini, apfiriye inyuma y’imisi ari mu gasho k’igipolisi
 Uyu mugore w’imyaka 22 ava mu gisagara ca Saqez kiri mu buraruko bushira uburengero, yahagaritswe i Tehran ku wa 13 z’uku kw’icenda n’abapolisi bajejwe imico myiza, bamwagiriza ko yahonyanze itegeko risaba abagore gupfuka imishatsi yabo na wa mwambaro wa hijab canke n’igitambara co mu mutwe
 Abategetsi ntibavuga aho aba banyabulaya bahagarikiwe ariko batanga uburorero cumi bavuga ko ari ubwo abanyamahanga bagizemwo uruhara hamwe n’imirwi itavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi iri hanze ifise uruhara muri ino myiyerekano
 Aba bahagaritswe bava mu bihugu vya Pologne, Suède, Ubudagi, Ubutaliyano, Ubufaransa hamwe n’Ubuholande, nk’uko ubushikiranganji bwa Irani bujejwe igendereza bubivuga
 Ibiro vy’ubuserukizi bw’Ubudagi, Ubufaransa, Ubwongereza n’ubwa Suède, biri mu vyagabishijwe ku ruhara rw’abakozi bavyo muri iyi myiyerekano yo kurwanya reta, nk’uko ubu bushikiranganji bubivuga
 Buvuga kandi ko imbere be n’igihe c’iyi myiyerekano, habanje kuba izindi nteguro nyinshi mu kuyitegurira canke kugira ngo bihurirane, harimwo ibitero nyabwonko hamwe n’ikwiragizwa “ry’amakuru y’ibinyoma ashigikira imigumuko” buvuga ko vyakorwa n’ibinyamakuru bitegamiye reta, nk’igisata ca BBC gikoresha ururimi rw’igi perse, hamwe na Iran International
 Uyu mugore Amini yaguye mw’ibohero yari yatwawemwo kugira ngo “yigishwe” akaba yapfiriye mu bitaro aho yari amaze imisi itatu yataye ubwenge (coma)
 Umuryango wiwe wemeza ko yakubiswe n’abapolisi ariko igipolisi kibandanya gishimangira ko yapfuye ahitanywe n’indwara y’umutima yamufashe giturumbuka
 Iran yagiriza “abansi b’abanyamahanga” ko bafise uruhara mu kaduruvayo kakurikiye, kakaba kamaze guhintana ababarirwa muri mirongo
 Mu biharuro vyaryo biheruka vyacishijwe ku rubuga rwa Twitter, ishirahamwe riharanira agateka ka zina muntu, Iran Human Rights (IHR), rifise icicaro muri Norvège/Norway, rivuga riti: "Abantu n’imiburiburi 83, harimwo n’abana, nibo bamaze kwemezwa ko bapfuye muri iyo migumuko ya Iran”
 Abandi 19 bavugwa ko bapfuye ejo ku wa gatanu inyuma y’imishamirano hagati y’igipolisi n’abari mu myiyerekano ku kirindiro c’igipolisi i Zahedan, umugwa mukuru w’intara ya Sistan-Baluchistan  iri mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko
 Muri aba bapfuye harimwo umukoroneri wo mu gisirikare, nk’uko vyandikwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP, n’aho bitashotse bimenyekana nimba iyi mishamirano ifitaniye isano n’iyo migumuko yatewe n’urupfu rwa Amini
 Buramatari w’intara Hossein Khiabani  yabwiye imboneshakure y’igihugu ati: "Abantu 19 barishwe abandi 20 barakomereka muri iyi mishamirano
 Uwushinzwe igendereza rya gisirikare mu ntara Koloneli Ali Mousavi nawe nyene yishwe”
 Intara ya Sistan-Baluchistan isanzwe ihana urubibe na Afghanistan hamwe na Pakistan ikunze kuberamwo imishamirano n’imirwi y’inkozi z’ikibi idandaza ibiyayuramutwe, hamwe n’inyeshamba zo mu nkehwa z’aba Baluchi hamwe n’imirwi y’intagondwa z’aba Islam bo mw’ishami ry’aba Sunni
 Mu gatondo k’ejo ku wa gatanu, ibinyamakuru vya reta vyatangaje ko inzego zijejwe umutekano zarasanye n’abitwaje ibirwanisho bari batye ikirindiro c’igipolisi i Zahedan

Ishirahamwe riharanira uburenganzira  ryasavye Fifa kuvana Iran mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe c’isi mu mupira  bw’amaguru inyuma yo kwankira abagore kurorera inkino mu gihugu cabo
 Iryo shirahamwe, Open Stadiums, ryabajije igituma igihugu cemererwa kuja mu mahiganwa mu gihe  abategetsi “n’ubu batarekurira abagore b’abanya-Iran kuraba urwo rukino rwiza
” Ako kamo gatewe haheze amayinga abagore bemerewe kuraba urukino rwo mu gihugu ubwa mbere kuva mu 1979
 Ariko iryo shirahamwe ntiryaheze amakenga ko ibibuga vy’umupira bizoguma vyuguruwe ku bagore
 Open Stadiums ryanditse mw’ikete yarungukiye umukuru wa Fifa  Gianni Infantino riti: “Abagore bo muri Iran ntibizeye baba abategetsi ba reta baba n’abategetsi b’ishirahamwe ry’umupira w’amaguru  ko ikibuga ca Azadi kizoguma cuguruye  ku bagore   igikombe c’isi ca Fifa 2022  ni camara kurangira itariki 18 Kigarama (12)"
 Rivuga kandi ko n’abazoja Qatar kuraba inkino bashobora kugira ingorane ku bategetsi ba Iran kuko bashobora kuguma bakurirana uwo wese azoba yagiye kuziraba
 Kubuza abagore kwitaba inkino biteye kubiri  n’amategeko mpuzamakungu y’umupira w’amaguru, nk’uko iryo kete ribivuga, rigashimika rivuga ko rero Fifa ikwiye guca ivana Iran mw’ihiganwa ry’igikombe 2022 muri Qatar
 Imbuga z’amakuru muri Iran zanditse ibivugwa ko abagore bemerewe kuraba urukino mu kwezi kw’umunani inyuma y’aho Fifa irungikiye ikete abategetsi ibasaba kwemerera abagore kwinjira mu bibuga vy’umupira
 Fifa yari imaze kubwira BBC ko itazoraba hirya kuri ico kibazo
 Nta tegeko rihari ribuza abagore kuja kuraba inkino  muri Iran, ariko ni imbonekarimwe kuko kenshi batemererwa kwinjira
 Imbere y’aho abagore ntibemererwa kuraba inkino zo mu gihugu aho abagabo baba bariko barakina kuko abajejwe kwigisha ijambo ry’imana batavyemera kw’izina rya Islam y’aba Shia
 Abagore baramaze kurorera inkino mpuzamakungu nkeya harimwo rumwe mu kwezi kwa gatatu uyu mwaka, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru, Reuters
 Iryo shirahamwe riharanira uburenganzira rivuga kandi ko umugwi w’abakinyi uzoja muri Qatar mu mpera z’uyu mwaka wihanijwe kutagira ico uvuze ko myiyerakano iriko irwagwamwo abantu muri iyi minsi muri Iran
 Yatewe n’urupfu rwa Mahsa Amini, umugore yapfuye ari mu minwe y’abaporisi inyuma yo gufatwa n’igiporisi kijejwe kwifata uko bibereye
 Iryo kete rivuga ko aho yapfiriye ari co kigo nyene “abafana b’abagore bakunze kujanwa bakaborezwa igufa iyo bubahutse bakaja kuraba urukino rw’umupira w’amaguru”

