 Iraswa ry’ibi bisasu - risanzwe riteye kubiri n’ibihano vya ONU - ribaye mu gihe Amerika na Korea y’Epfo biri mu myimenyerezo rusangi ya gisirikare mu mazi y’inyanja izungurutse ikigwa ca Korea
 Abategetsi ba Korea y’Epfo n’ab’Ubuyapani bariyamiriza aka “gasomborotso”
 Bubaye ubwa kabiri mu ndwi imwe gusa Korea ya Ruguru igerageza ibisasu vya misire muri uno mwaka umaze kuberamwo ibikorwa vy’igerageza ry’ibirwanisho gusumba iyindi myaka yose
 Ribaye kandi mu gihe kidasanzwe – mu rugendo rwiwe muri Korea y’Epfo, umupfasoni Harris azoshika ku rubibe hamwe no muri ka karere katemerewemwo ibikorwa vya gisirikare (Demilitarised Zone, DMZ) ariko gacungerewe cane kagabuza izi Korea zompi
 Ejo ku wa gatatu, yashikirije ijambo ingabo za Amerika ku kirindiro cazo co mu Buyapani, aho yiyamirije ibikorwa biheruka vya Pyongyang vyo kugerageza ibirwanisho, hamwe “n’umugambi utemewe n’amategeko wo guhingura ibirwanisho uteye akaga ku mutekano w’akarere”
 Mu gihe ibiganiro hagati ya Korea ya Ruguru na korea y’Epfo vyerekeye guhagarika umugambi wo guhingura ibirwanisho vy’ubumara vyahagaze, mu gihe kandi izi mpande zompi zibandanya zikomeza ibisata vyazo vyo kwivuna abansi, ibi bikorwa vy’igerageza ni bimwe mu bituma ibintu vyunyuka cane
 Ibikorwa vyo muri ino ndwi vy’igerageza ry’ibirwanisho – ica mbere kikaba cabaye ku wa Mungu imbere y’uko iyi myimenyerezo ya gisirikare y’ibisata birwanira mu mazi itangura – ni ivya mbere kuva mu ntango z’ukwa gatandatu, ariko Korea ya Ruguru imaze kugerageza ibirwanisho birenga 30 gushika ubu muri uno mwaka, kurusha mu yindi myaka yose
 Abategetsi ba Korea y’Epfo bavuga ko igerageza ry’izi misire ejo ku wa gatatu ryabahe hagati y’isaha 18:10 na 18:20 mu masaha yo muri ako karere, bikaba vyarashwe ku ntera y’ibirometero 360, bikaba kandi vyagurutse gushika ku birometero 30 uja hejuru
 Abajejwe gucungera imbibe b’Ubuyapani nabo nyene barabonye ibi bisasu
 Abakuru ba gisirikare ba Korea y’Epfo basohoye itangazo bavuga bati: "Aka gasomborotso ka Korea ya Ruguru kazotuma ibikorwa vya Korea y’Epfo na Amerika vyo kuzibira no kwivuna bikomezwa, kandi nta kindi bizovamwo atari kubandanya bikumira Korea ya Ruguru ku rubuga mpuzamakungu”
 Abahinga babona ko ibi bikorwa vy’igerageza ari ukwihora ku myimenyerezo rusangi ya gisirikare y’ibisata vya gisirikare birwanira mu mazi mu gihe Washington na Seoul biriko bikomeza igisata co kwivuna abansi ca Korea y’Epfo – iyi myimenyerezo rusangi ni iya mbere ibaye harimwo ubwato bwa Amerika  butwara indege kuva mu 2017
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije inama ya bose mu ntango z’ino ndwi, uwuserukira Pyongyang mw’ishirahamwe ONU, Song Kim, yaraneguye Amerika na Korea y’Epfo kuri ino myimenyerezo yabo, avuga ko yariko ituma iki kigwa “cegereza intambara”
 Yavuze ko “poritike y’urwanko” ya Amerika kuri Korea ya Ruguru ari yo mvo isi ubu “iriko itera ija mu bihe bibi cane”
 Korea y’Epfo na Amerika vyamye vyishigikira mu myimenyerezo yavyo rusangi, bikavuga ko ifise intumbero yo kuzana ituze mu karere
 Amakuru avuga ko iki gihugu ca gikomunista gisanzwe gikorera mw’ibanga coba gitunze ibirwanisho vy’ubumara, abandanya yiyongera – ibi bikaba biteye umutima uhagaze Amerika na Korea y’Epfo
 Mu ntango z’uku kwezi, Korea ya Ruguru yemeje itegeko ryemeza ko ari igihugu gitunze ibirwanisho vy’ubumara
 Indongozi yayo Kim Jong-un  yariyemeje ko igihugu ciwe kitazokwigera giheba umugambi waco wo guhingura ibirwanisho canke ngo citabe ibiganiro bifise intumbero yo kukibuza gutunga ibirwanisho vy’ubumara
 Iri tegeko kandi ryemerera Korea ya Ruguru kurasa ubwa mbere, mu bihe bitari bike bishobora gushika
 Gushika mu misi iheze, camye kivuga ko ibirwanisho vyaco ari ivyo kwikingira, mu ntumbero yo gukinga intambara
 Haraciye amezi ibisata vy’igendereza vya Amerika na Korea y’Epfo bivuga ko Korea ya Ruguru yiteguye kugerageza ikirwanisho c’ubumara ariko ko irindiriye akanya keza ka poritike
 Iri ryoba ari igerageza rigize indwi ry’ikirwanisho c’ubumara, rikazoba kandi ribaye irya mbere mu myaka itanu
 Ejo ku wa gatatu, igisata ca Korea y’Epfo kijejwe igendereza cabwiye abanyaporitike ko iri gerageza ry’ikirwanisho c’ubumara rishobora kuba hagati y’ukwezi kw’icumi n’ukw’icumi na rimwe, mu kiringo kiri hagati y’ikoraniro ry’umugambwe Chinese Party Congress be n’amatora y’abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka muri Amerika
 Perezida Yoon Suk-yeol wa Korea y’Epfo, kuva ashitse ku butegetsi mu kwa gatanu, yibanze gukomeza ugukorera hamwe hagati ya korea y’Epfo na Amerika mu ntumbero yo kwirinda akaga gaterwa na Korea ya Ruguru

Umukuru w'Uburusiya Vladmir Putin ku wa gatanu azokora ibirori vyo kwomeka icese ku Burusiya  izindi ntara zine za Ukraine inyuma y’amatora ya kamarampaka yakoresheje akiyamirizwa na Ukraine n’amakungu nk’amanyanga
 Abategetsi bashigikiye Uburusiya muri izo ntara imbere yaho bari bavuze ko ayo matora yamaze iminsi itanu yatumye abanyagihugu hafi bose bashigikira iyo ntumbero
 Ivyo vyitwa amatora yabaye muri Luhansk na Donetsk mu buseruko, hamwe na Zaporizhzhia na  Kherson mu bumanuko
 Umukuru w’Uburusiya azoshikiriza ijambo rikomeye ku biro vyiwe Kremlin
 Aho kuremeshereza ibirori haja hamaze gutegurwa ku kibanza citwa Place Rouge/Red Square ku murwa mukuru Moscou aho ivyapa bivuga ko izo ntara zine zibaye igice c’Uburusiya bija vyamaze kumanikwa, hakaba hategekanijwe kandi igiteramo c’umuziki kuri uwo mugoroba
 Ivyo birori vyibutsa ivy’igihe intara ya Crimea yomekwa ku Burusiya mu 2014, naho nyene bikaba vyakurikiye amatora ya kamarampaka atemewe, n’ico gihe umukuru w’igihugu akaba yari yabanje gushikiriza ijambo igihugu
 Uko kwiyomekako intara ya Crimea n’ubu ntikwigeze kwemerwa n’igice kinini c’amakungu
 Ntibiremezwa niba n’ubu prezida Putin azoshikiriza iryo jambo ari ahagaragara  nk’ico gihe
 Umuvugizi w’umukuru w’Uburusiya Dmitry Preskov yavuze ati: “Ejo isaha icenda [yo mu Burusiya, isaha 6 canke sasita  kw’isaha mpuzamakungu ya GMT], mu cumba ca St George mu kirimba ca Grand Kremlin Palace, hazoba ibirori vyo gushira umukono ku ngingo yo kwomeka ku Burusiya intara nshasha”
 Babiri mu bategetsi b’izo ntara bashigikiye ukwiyonkora kuri Ukraine bitezwe kuzoba bahari
 Umukuru w’Uburusiya yitezwe gushikiriza ijambo riri ukwaryo inama nkenguzamateka itariki 4 za Gitugutu (10), iminsi itatu imbere y’isabukuru y’imyaka 70 kuva avutse
 Inama nshingamateka izogira uruhara kandi mu kwemeza uko kwiyomekako izo ntara za Ukraine ahanini kwiyamirijwe n’amakungu
 Nta buryo bwigenga bwabaye bwo gucungera ayo matora kandi hagiye hatangwa amakuru y’uko abajejwe amatora bagenda baraca ku nzu ku nzu baherekejwe n’abasirikare bafise ibigwanisho
 Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuze ko zizofatira ibihano Uburusiya kubera izo kamarampaka z’amanyanga, mu gihe ibihugu vy’ishirahamwe rya Buraya biriko biriga urutonde rugira umunani rw’ingingo zofatirwa Uburusiya, harimwo ibihano ku muntu wese yagize uruhara muri ayo matora
 Umushikiranganji w’Ubudagi ajejwe imigeneranire Annalena Baerbock yavuze ku wa kane ko abantu bo mu turere twa Ukraine twigaruriwe bavanywe mu ngo zabo canke aho bakorera kw’iterabwoba kandi rimwe rimwe bafatiweko inkoho
 Ati: “Ico ni igihushane c’amatora yo mu mwidegemvyo kandi atarenganya
 Kandi ico ni igihushane c’amahoro, n’amahoro y’agahato
” Ayo matora yabaye mu turere tungana na 15% tw’igihugu cose ca Ukraine abanyagihugu babimenyeshejwe ku munota wa nyuma
 Ibinyamakuru vyo mu Burusiya vyavuze ko kwitwaza abasirikare bafise ibigwanisho vyakozwe ku mvo z’umutekano, ariko vyaragaragaye ko vyongereje gushira igitutu ku banyagihugu
 Umugore umwe muri Enerhodar yabwiye BBC ati: “Wishura ku munwa hanyuma abasirikare bakandika inyishu ku rupapuro bagaca barugumya
” Uburusiya izo ntara zine bugiye kwiyomekako nta n’imwe bugenzura ijana kw’ijana
 N’ubwo igice kinini ca Luhansk kiri mu minwe y’Uburusiya, Moscou igenzura 60% ya Donetsk
 Inyuma y’amezi indwi kuva Uburusiya buteye Ukraine buhereye mu buraruko, mu buseruko no mu bumanuko, intambara n’ubu iracabica bigacika ku rwasiro rwayo muri ivyo bice vyose
 Umurwa mukuru w’intara ya Zaporizhzhia uri mu minwe ya reta ya Ukraine, hanyuma igitero co kugaruza uturere kikaba kiriko kiraba muri Kherson
 N’ubwo abategetsi bashizweho n’Uburusiya bagumye basaba ko izo ntara zomekwa ku Burusiya, intambwe za gisirikare Ukraine yateye mu kwezi kw’icenda zitegerezwa kuba zararemereye ubutegetsi bw’Uburusiya
 Ingabo za Ukraine zaragaruje uturere tutari duke mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko, ku wa kane naho zikaba zavuze ko zagose ingabo z’Uburusiya mu gisagara ca Lyman gikomeye ku mikenyuro ya gisirikare muri Donetsk
 Mu ndwi iheze, Vladmir Putin yahamagaje ingabo z’integabizoza aca akangisha ko hazokoreshwa uburyo bwose afise, harimwo n’ibigwanisho vya nucleaire, mu kurwanira ico afata nk’ubutaka bw’Uburusiya
 Aho azoca ashobora kuvuga ko ubutaka bw’Uburusiya butewe n’ibigwanisho vy’iburengarazuba, akaba yizigiye ko ivyo bizotuma hari ibihugu bihagarika imfashanyo ya gisirikare biha Ukraine
 Ariko umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe imigenderanire yagabishije avuga ko iryo kinamico ry’amatora ataco rizohindura ku rugamba

Umunyamuziki w’igihangange, umunya-Colombia Shakira agiye kurengutswa mu butungane bwa Espagne yagirizwa gukwepa kuriha amakori yababa imiriyoni 14,5 z’ama euro
 Sentare yo muri Barcelona yategetse ko uyu muririmvyi arengutswa ku vyaha bitandatu yagirizwa, n’aho ata tariki yamenyeshejwe
 Abashikirizamanza ba Espagne bashaka ko uyu munyamuziki rurangirnwa  apfungwa imyaka umunani, yongere atozwe n’ihadabu ry’imiriyoni 23,8 z’ama euro mu gihe yokwagirwa n’icaha
 Uyu muririmyi w’imyaka 45 abandanya ahakana ivyo yagirizwa
 Mu kiganiro aheruka kugiriranira n’ikinyamakuru Elle co muri Espagne, yavuze ati:  "Ndizeye ko mfise ivyemezo bikwiye kugira ngo niregure kandi ko ubutungane buzonyeza”
 Mw’itangazo ryabo, ababuranira Shakira bavuga ko bazokora ico bajejwe “mu kwerekana ivyemezo mu gihe nyaco”
 Yabanje kwanka umwumvikano n’abashikirizamanza, ahitamwo kuja mu butungane
 Uru rubanza ruhagaze ku kirego kijanye n’aho yabaye hagati ya 2012 na 2014, igihe abashikirizamanza bamwagirije ko yaba muri Espagne ariko akaba yandikishije ko yaba ahandi
 Mu mategeko ya Espagne, abantu babaye mu gihugu amezi arenga atandatu bafatwa ko ari abantu bategerezwa kuriha amakori
 Ariko Shakira avuga ko ataba muri Espagne
 Mu kw’indwi, abashikirizamanza basohoye urwandiko rwavuga ko yari yaguze inzu muri Barcelona mu 2012, yahavuye iba iyo kubamwo we n’umukunzi wiwe ico gihe, umukinyi w’umupira w’amaguru wa Barcelona, Gerard Piqué
 Abamuburanira bavuga ko gushika mu 2014 amatungo yiwe hafi yose yava mu ngendo yakora kw’isi kandi ko ibihe vyinshi yabimaze hanze ya Espane
 Yabwiye ikinyamakuru Elle ati: "Abajejwe kwegeranya amakori muri Espagne babonye ko ndiko ndareshanya n’umunyagihugu wa Espagne baca batangura kumira amate
 Biragaragara ko bashaka gukurikirana aya mahera uko vyogenda kwose”
 Shakira yatangaje ko Espagne ari co gihugu arihiramwo amakori yiwe mu 2015
 Avuga ko yari yarishe ikori ry’imiriyoni 17,2  z’ama euro kandi ko ata madeni yari asigaranye
 Mu rundi rubanza mu 2019, sentare y’igihugu muri Espagne yatoje Piqué ihadabu ry’imiriyoni 2,1 z’ama euro kubera ukutariha amakori hagati ya 2008 na 2010
 Mu ntango z’ukwa gatandatu uno mwaka, aba bantu niho batangaza ko bari bavanye inyuma y’imyaka 11
 Piqué na Shakira bafitaniye abana babiri b’abahungu, uwa mbere afise imyaka icenda, uwa kabiri imyaka indwi
 Mu kiganiro yagiranye na Elle niho yatangaza ubwa mbere ivyo gutandukana kwabo, aho yabwiye iki kinyamakuru ko yari “mu kibazo  gishobora kuba kiri mu bibazo bikomeye cane, ibihe bibi cane mu buzima bwanje”

Peter Musembi B﻿BC Sport “Kuri twebwe  iwacu muri muri Tanzania, kari kuba kabaye akaga
” Se w’umunya-Tanzania wa mbere yaronse umudari wa Olympic mu kwoga ariko arayaga n’umukobwa wiwe, yemera ukuri, agerageza kumusigurira igituma yamuhishije ingorane y’amagara yishe nibura batanu bo mu muryango wabo
 Iyo ngorane – kubera kudasuzumwa – yatumye kunyarukanwa kwa muganga mu mpera z’umwaka uheze, ico gihe havanwa  mu nda ya Magdalena Moshi  ibiro hafi bine (4kg)  vy’ibivyimba bita fibromes  inyuma yo gukorwa (kubagwa) vyihuta
 Imisi y’ububabare yaciye ikurikira imyaka n’iyindi  yari amaze yama agenda yumva atamerewe neza kuva mu myaka ya mbere yiwe y’ubuyabaga, aho akaba yari afise iyo ngorane ata nkeka ko yahungabanije umwuga wiwe wo kwoga
 None, kubera iki Alex, se wiwe, atigeze amubwira na kimwe ku bijanye n’ibivyimba vya fibromes mu muryango wabo? Ati: “Abantu barashobora guca batangura gutungwa urutoke ngo ni intavyara” imbere yo kwongerako ati: “Ni rumwe mu mpome z’Abanya-Afrika dukeneye kumenya ko zihari kugirango dushobore kuzisenyura
” Mu kugira ico akoze, Magdalena yiyemeje kurwanya umuco wo kutubahuka kuvuga ibibazo vy’amagara ajanye n’irondoka (santé  reproductive/ reporoductive health) mu gihugu ciwe za Tanzania
 Kuko, bwabaye ubwa mbere, igihe yariko arakira inyuma yo kubagwa muri Australia iyo yari yagiye kwiga, amenya ko yari afise ingorane ya fibromes kandi yari  isanzwe iri mu muryango iwabo kuva kera, mu gihe kandi ishobora guhererakanywa mu muryango
 N’ubwo yajanwa mu bitaro kenshi ku murwa mukuru Dar Es Salaam afise ingorane zijanye n’irondoka  mu myaka yiwe ya mbere y’ubuyabaga, ubwoba bwo gutungwa agatoki kubera fibromes bwatumye kuba Magdalena ashobora kuba afise iyo ngorane babimunyegeza
 “Nibaza ko ata gice canje na kimwe kizokwigera kibabarira uwo muco wo gukora ivyo”, niko uwo mugore w’imyaka 32 yabwiye BBC Sport Africa ari i muhira iwe hashasha muri Adelaide, muri Australia
 TURAGABISHIJE:  Iyi nkuru irimwo ifoto yerekana uko vyakabaye ibivyimba (fibromes) vyavanywe muri Magdalena Moshi
 Magdalena yanyarukanywe kwa muganga muri Nyakanga/Nzeri (9) mu 2021 inyuma yo kwumva ububabare bw’umurengera mu ntantu igihe yari mu nzu yo kwinonora imitsi (gym)
 “Nibuka ikintu ca mbere numvise nikanguye n’uko umuganga asinziriza yariko aravuga  ngo ‘Kirya kivyimba cari kinini – cari cashitse mu mbavu!”’ nk’uko vyibukwa n’umugore ariko araca urupauro rw’umutsindo rwa PhD mu vyigwa vy’amagara
 Nk’uko yahavuye abimenya ubwiwe, fibromes ni ibivyimba bitarimwo cancer biza mu gitereko canke iruhande yaco kandi kenshi bikaza mu myaka umukobwa aba ashobora kurondoka (ashobora kuvyara)
 Iyo ngorane ishikira abagore b’abanya-Afrika  kurusha abandi bose, umuganga wa Magdalena akaba yamubwiye ko amamuko yiwe y’ubunya-Afrika yatumye “ibivyimba vyiwe vyinshi vya fibromes vyagiye kumenyekana bitevye’
 Muganga Tran Nguyen yabwiye BBC Sport Africa ati :’’Abagore b’abamamuko ya Afrika bafise ivyago bingana incuro zibiri gushika kuri zitatu zo kugira fibromes kurusha bagenzi babo b’abazungukazi”
 Amaze kuva mu bitaro, Moshi yaronse terefone ya se wiwe Alex, muri Tanzania, amuhishurira ko fibromes ari ingorane iri mu muryango hanyuma amubwira arira ko yicuza kuba yarabimuhishije
 Aca yongerako ati: “Kwumva ko igituma umuryango wa data utavuga ico kibazo ari ukubera  fibromes zijanye no gutera kutavyara, gutuma inda zikoroka no kuvyara abana bapfuye - no kwumva ko bene ivyo bintu vyari kumbuza amahirwe yo gushobora kuronka umugabo
 “Intumbero ni ukubinuma, bakurungike kurongorwa hanyuma ico kibazo uzomenye ingene ucifatanwo mu nyuma
” Ubu Moshi ariko aragirirwa ubuhinga bw’uko imbuto z’umugabo n’izo umugore zihurizwa hanze (In Vitro Fertilization, IVF), hanyuma zigaca zijanwa mu gitereko mu gihe be n’umuhungu bakundana bariko baragerageza kuronka umwana
 Moshi yabaye umunya-Tanzania wa mbere akiri muto yaronse umudari wa Olympic igihe yawutsindira mu nkino za Beijing 2008  ku myaka 16
 Yarahiganywe kandi mu nkino za 2012 na 2016 ariko ntiyigeze arenga intambwe ya mbere kuko uretse ko yarwana n’abakeba, yarwana kandi  n’ububabare bwo mu mugongo butahera
 Avuga ati: “Mu nyuma niho nagiye kumenya ko kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye vya fibromes ari ukubabara umugongo
” “Ingene vyanyononeye umwuga wo kwoga, numva  mu mutwe `ntashaka no gusubira kuvyiyumvira kuko vyombabaza cane”
 Igihe yariko arakira aho bamukoze, Magdalena – n’ubu acitaba amahiganwa yo kwoga – yarahamagaye se kuri video kugira bavugane ico kibazo
 Mu gihe yari yarengewe n‘ivyashitse, yashaka kumenya igihe se yari amaze azi ko fibromes ari ingorane iri mu  muryango, igituma yakomeje kubimuhisha kandi Magdalena yaguma yerekana ibimenyetso  mu myaka ya mbere y’ubuyabaga hamwe n’ivyigwa umuryango ushobora kuvanamwo
 BBC Sport Africa yemerewe gukurikira  ico kiyago
  Vyashotse bigaragara ko Alex yari amaze imyaka myinshi azi ko abantu ba hafi mu muryango bari barivuje ama fibromes, harimwo babiri babanje kubagwa nk’uko vyagendeye Magdalena
 "Urumva ikibazo nari nsanzwe ndakizi, kandi nzi ko cama kijana no kuvyara
 Mu nyuma narabuze abandi bavyara, mu nyuma ndamenya ko na mama yari afise ingorane nk’izo
” Abajijwe igituma ibibazo vya Magdalena bijanye n’irondoka mu gihe c’ubuyabaga no kwama ariko araja kwa muganga itabaye imvo ikwiye kugira bahishure ikibazo, Alex yishuye ati: “Hari ibintu bitavugwa hagati y’umukobwa na se
” “Mu mico yacu, ku bijanye no kurongorwa, abantu akenshi bagerageza guhisha aho bafise ingorane
 Mu mibereho yacu, vyamye bimeze nk’ikibazo co kwigwanako – bisigura ko wama ugerageza kurondera uwo mwubakana akomeye neza cane bishoboka
” “Kubera izo mvo, vyinshi muri ivyo bintu mu mico yacu vyarahishwa
 "Ku binyerekeye, nabaye nka ya nyoni bita autruche  - iyo autruche  ifise ingorane, inyegeza umutwe, ikibaza ko umutumba wayo wose ata ngorane uja kugira
 Nibaza ko natwe bizotungendera neza
 Ntivyigeze biba uko
”  Ivyashitse vyatumye Alex asubira kwibaza ico yokora kuri uwo muco wo guhakana no kuguma mu gacerere muri Tanzania
 Ubu ibitahora bivugwa arabivuga akaba yarabwiye abakobwa n’abagore bose bakiri bato mu muryango wiwe kugenda kwipimisha barabe ko ata vyago bafise vyo kugira fibromes canke izindi ngorane zijanye n’irondoka
 Ubwo butumwa yaranabushikanye  mu muryango iyo  avuka, ku mucamo w’umusozi Kilimanjaro mu buraruko bwa Tanzania
 Igihe bariko barayaga, Alex yabwiye Magalena ati iyo apfa yari kuba ibaye ingaruka ya mbere mbi – ariko ko kudashora kuronka abana vyari kuba “akaga”
 Mu nyuma Mgadalena aramubaza ati: “None wamerewe gute wumvise ko ubwa mbere , fibromes zagarutse hanyuma ubwa kabiri, ko bariko barankorera IVF  kubera ivyo?” “Amajambo yaramperanye
” Magdakena we ntiyamuheranye, kandi avuga ko azobandanya guharanira ko haba ibiyago ku magara ajanye no kurondoka muri Afrika
 Inyuma y’ingorane ziwe, yararondeye adatevye abo mu muryango bashobora kuba bafise ingorane nk’izo, kandi nabo batubahuka kuzivuga
 Yasiguye ati: “Narahamagaye  bavyaranje bose ndababira ko mfise ico kibazo kandi ndabumvisha ko bategerezwa kwipimisha
” “Ubutumwa bwanje ku bakobwa n’abagore bakiri bato muri Afrika y’Ubuseruko na Afrika yose  ni ubu: niba ufise ingorane z’amagara afatiye kw’irondoka, ntibituma ubugore bwawe bugabanuka, rero bivuge hanyuma urondere ubufasha
” Aho ashoboreye kuzibira ivyago vyari gushikira abo mu muryango wiwe batari bafise amahirwe nk’ayiwe, Magdalena ubu ariko atera iyindi ntambwe, yizigiye ko gutuma abantu bamenya ivyerekeye fibromes muri Tanzania no mu bindi bihugu bishobora gufasha abandi mu kuvanaho ivyo gutinya gutungwa agatoki
 Gutinya gutungwa agatoki vyatumye yoga ukuboko kumwe gufashe mu mongongo, mu nkino no mu buzima
 “Vyashize  amagara yanje ku gihe kirekire, ubuzima bwanje  n’ubushobozi bwanje bwo kuronka abana mu ngorane zikomeye”

Abantu b’ikigwati ca Sohagpur, mu ntara ya Bihar mu buraruko bw’Ubuhindi bagize umunsi mukuru wo kwigina ko umwe muri bo yaronse akazi ka reta, akaba abaye uwa mbere mu myaka 75
 Rakesh Kumar w’imyaka 30 yaronse akazi ko kuba umwigisha mw’ishure ry’intango rya reta
 Ababa muri ico kigwati batanze imbombo basukira kandi pudere y’amabara mu munezero kuva aho bumviye iyo nkuru ku ndwi iheze
 Ubuzi bwa reta buraronderwa cane mu Buhindi kuko butekanye  kandi butanga akarusho
 Ikigwati Kumar   abamwo gisanzwe kirimwo ishure rya reta, ariko abagisha baryo bose bava mu bindi bice vy’iyo ntara
 Devendra Chowdhary, umwigisha waho, avuga ko  haheze imyaka myinshi abantu barondera akazi kobahemba neza – kuva mu 1947, igihe Ubuhindi bwaronka intahe y’ubwigenge – ariko amahirwe ntiyababana menshi
 Abanyeshure benshi baragenda kwiga mu bisagara bikuru bikuru, ariko nta n’umwe yari bwashobore kuronka akazi ka reta -gushika ubu
 Chowdhary avuga ko kuba Kumar yaronse akazi “ aho vyabereye avanyeho igicu cirabura c’amahirwe make muri ico kigwati” kandi ko “abakiri bato bazoterwa intege n’amahirwe yagize”
 Kumar avuga ko yumva anezerewe cane kuba yatumye ikigwati ciwe cumva ko cishimye
 Ariko abandanya avuga ko urugendo rwiwe rutamworoheye na gato
 Uwo mugabo yahora agenda n’ikinga ku birometero birenga 30 kugira ashike kw’ishure ryisumbuye
 Se wiwe yari asanzwe acuruza ivyo kurya
 Avuga ko aho apfiriye, ibintu vyaciye bigorana gusumba
 Avuga ati: “Ariko naritaye ku rutare kugira nshitse icifuzo ca data – yashaka ko mba umuganga canke umwigisha
 Ubu rero icifuzo  ciwe nagishize mu ngiro
” Kumar yizeye ko ako kazi gashasha kazomwugururira  ayandi mahirwe

Umupatiri wa Ekleziya Katolika mu buraruko bwa Tanzania yarengukishijwe imbere y’ubutungane yagirizwa ivya mfura mbi yakoreye abana, nk’uko bivugwa n’igipolisi
 Aba bana ni abanyeshure bo kuva mu mwaka wa gatandatu gushika mu mwaka wa mbere w’ishure ryisumbuye bariko bitegurira gusangira, abandi gukomezwa
 Umunyamabanga mukuru w’Inama nkuru y’Abepiskopi muri Tanzania, Patiri Charles Kitima, avuga ko Ekleziya izokorana n’ababijejwe kugira ngo ubutungane bukore muri uru rubanza
 Patiri Kitima ati: “Twavuze ko turindiriye iyo ngingo [ya sentare] kugira ngo izindi ngingo zifatwe


ivyemezo ni bitangwe hanyuma nawe ahabwe akaryo ko kwiregura, ico nico turindiriye
 “Ni ngombwa ko amategeko akora igikorwa cayo kandi Ekleziya izokwifatanya n’ababijejwe kugira ngo abakorewe ikibi batunganirizwe”
 Patiri Kitima yabwiye BBC ko muri rusangi Ekleziya Katorika irwanya ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina rikorerwa abana kuko isengero ritegerezwa kuba ikibanza c’amahoro kuri bose
 Ati: “Reka twemere ko iki ari ikibazo kijanye na kamere ya nyene kubikora, dufise abapatiri barenga 3
000 muri kino gihugu ariko muri bo harimwo abo usanga bafise utunenge n’intege nke, ivyo bibaho”
 Patiri Kitima avuga ko iki ari akabi kabishe kuko gituma abavyeyi n’abana bagira impungenge nyinshi, abana iyo bagiye mu bikorwa nk’ivyo baba bizeye ko bagiye guhura n’umuntu yari kubarera muri mutima
 Ati: “Rero iyo bakorewe ibitabajanye ni ibintu bibabaza cane
 “Twebwe nka Ekleziya turababazwa n’ingeso mbi z’umuntu umw’umwe ziteye kubiri kubiri n’ico twategerezwa kwubaka, kwubaka umuntu mu mico myiza
 “Ureste ko iki ari igicumuro kandi kibabaza Imana, gifise n’ingaruka mbi ku bana, rero ni ngombwa ko hafatwa ingingo ruhasha”
 Patiri Kitima avuga ko kw’isi abantu nk’abo bahari, ko rero dutegerezwa gufashanya nk’abanya muryango mu guhindura izo ngeso, kandi tugatanga inkuru iyo hari ikintu nk’iki kibaye
 Avuga ko uburyo bwo gutanga inkuru muri Ekleziya butomoye, kuva hasi gushika hejuru ku Nama nkuru y’abepiskopi, abantu b’abahinga mu gutorera inyishu ibibazo nk’ivyo

Ubuyapani bwagirije inzego z’Uburusiya zijejwe umutekano ko zaboshe igitambara mu maso abakozi bayo bo mu biro vy’ubuserukizi zongera zirabapfunga mu gisagara ca Vladivostok  kiri mu buseruko
 Motoki Tatsunori aserukira ico gihugu muri ico gisagara, yarekuwe kuri uno wa kabiri, inyuma yo gupfungwa yagirizwa kwabura – aca ahabwa amasaha 48 yo kuva mu Burusiya
 Moscou ivuga ko yahawe amakuru y’ibanga ku bijanye n’imigenderanire n’igihugu co ku mugabane wa Aziya itavuze izina
 Ubuyapani burahakana ivyo yagirizwa bugasaba iki gihugu gusaba imbabazi ku mugaragaro
 Igisata c’Uburusiya kijejwe igendereza FSB kivuga ko capfunze Tatsunori ku wa mbere inyuma y’aho afatiwe ariko arondera amakuru ajanye “n’ingaruka z’ibihano vy’ibihugu vy’uburengero”  kuri Moscou inyuma y’aho itereye Ukraine muri Ruhuhuma/Gashyantare  (ukwezi kwakabiri)
 Iki gisata casohoye itangazo kivuga kiti: "Umuyapani akora mu buserukizi yarapfunzwe afatanywe itonga ariko ahabwa amakuru akiri mw’ibanga ku mafaranga, ku vyerekeye imigenderanire y’Uburusiya n’ikindi gihugu kiri mu karere ka Aziya na Pasific”
 Ariko Ubuyapani buvuga ko ipfungwa ry’umuserukizi wabwo ku mvo za poritike ryahonyanze amasezerano ya Vienne ku bijanye n’imigenderanire kandi ryakozwe “hakoreshejwe iterabwoba”
 Umunyamabanga mukuru wa reta, Hirokazu Matsuno , yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Uyu mutegetsi yaboshwe igitambara mu maso, bamukandamiza  amaboko n’umutwe ku buryo atashoboye no kwinyiganyiza igihe yari apfunzwe, yongera kandi abazwa ibibazo akankamirwa”
 Avuga ko Ubuyapani “bwiyamirije bwivuye inyuma ibi bikorwa bigayitse” aca yemeza ko uyu mutegetsi wo mu buserukizi azova mu Burusiya hatarenze ku wa gatatu inyuma y’aho yirukaniwe
 Ubuyapani buteye kubiri n'igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine kandi bufatrwa nk'umwansi n'Uburusiya – co kimwe na Amerika, Ubwongereza n’ibindi bihugu bishigikiye Ukraine

Uyu wa kabiri niwo musi wa nyuma w’amatora ariko abera mu turere twa Ukraine turi mu minwe y’Uburusiya, amatora Kyiv n’incuti zayo z’Uburengero bafata ko ari amanyanga
 Intara za Donetsk na Luhansk mu buseruko, hamwe na Kherson na Zaporizhzhia mu bumanuko ziri muri ano “matora ya kamarampaka” yatanguye ku wa 23 akaba yiteze kurangira kuri uno wa 27 Nyakanga (9), abanyagihugu bagahamagarirwa kwemeza canke guhakana nimba bakwiye kwegukira Uburusiya
 Abategetsi ntibagenzura vyuzuye intara n’imwe muri izi, ariko ibi ntibibabuza gutangaza ko abantu bayitabiriye ku bwinshi kandi ko abanyagihugu bipfuza kwegukira Uburusiya
 Mu misi y’amatora ine iheze abategetsi baherekejwe n’ababacungereye bafise inkoho bazunguruka urugo ku rugo bategeka abantu gutora, uno musi abanyagihugu bababa imiriyoni zine  muri izo ntara bakaba basabwa gushika ku biro vy’amatora kugira ngo batore, maze bemeze canke bahakane umugambi wo kwegukira Uburusiya
 Kuri Ukraine, aya matora ya kamarampaka asigura ko ibiganiro vy’amahoro n’Uburusiya ari ikintu kitagishobotse
 Mu gihe Uburusiya bwokwigarurira burundu izi ntara zigize ibice15% vya Ukraine yose, bishobora gutuma iyi ntambara igera ku rugero rushasha kandi ruteye ubwoba, aho Moscou yofata ko igitero ico ari co cose Ukraine yokora irondera kuzibohoza coba ari ukuvogera ubutaka bwayo
 Inkoho zari zihari zari izo kugukingira uriko uratora, canke zari izo kugutera ubwoba ngo utore? Iki nico kibazo cari mu mitwe y’abantu muri ino misi, aho abategetsi baherekejwe n’abasirikare, baca ku rugo ku rundi
 Serhiy Haidai, buramatari wa Luhansk yahunze, yagiriza abategetsi bashaka kwiyonkora ko bafuse amazina y’abantu batoye banka kwegukira Uburusiya canke banse gutora
 Asubwirwamwo n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters, avuga ati: “Abaserukira ingabo zateye igihugu baca ku nzu ku nzu bafise amasandugu y’amatora
 Aya ni amatora aba mw’ibanga, sivyo?”
 Mu kindi kiganiro yagiranye n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Associated Press, avuga ko Abarusiya bakoresheje ano matora nk’icitwazo, mu ntumbero yo kurondera abagabo bashobora kwinjiza mu gisirikare, be no gusaka barondera “ikintu ico ari co cose giteye amakenga kandi cegukira Ukraine”
 Umugore umwe yabwiye BBC ingene abavyeyi biwe batoye mu gisagara ca Melitopol mu ntara ya Zaporizhzhia
 Avuga ko “abantu babiri bifatanije n’umwansi” bashitse ku nzu babamwo bari kumwe n’abasirikare babiri b’Abarusiya bakabaha ikarata y’itora kugira batereko igikumu
 Uyu mugore ati: “Dawe yanditse ‘oya’
 Mama yari ahagaze iruhande yiwe, abaza igishobora kuba mu gihe yoshirako ‘oya’
 Bamwishuye bati, ‘Nta na kimwe’
 Ubu, mama avuga ko afise ubwoba ko Abarusiya bazobatoteza”
 Uwundi mugore ari mu gisagara ca Enerhodar, ari naho ikigo ca nikleyeri ca Zaporizhzhia kiri, yabwiye BBC ati: “Wishura n’umunwa hanyuma uyo musirikare w’Uburusiya akandika ku rukaratasi inyishu utanze agaca arugumya”
 Umunyamakuru wa Ukraine Maxim Eristavi yanditse kuri Twitter ko umuryango wiwe wategetswe “gutora ku nguvu bawurabishijeko inkoho” mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Yandika ati: “Baraza ku nzu yawe
 Utegerezwa gutera ikimenyetso ku kadirisha kemeza ko ushaka kwegukira Uburusiya (canke naho kuguma uri umunya-Ukraine mu gihe ushaka kwiyahura)
 Ibi vyose ni mu gihe aba babacungereye bafise n’inkoho baba bariko barakuraba”
 Petro Kobernik yahunze ava muri Kherson imbere y’uko amatora atangura, yabwiye AP mu kiganiro yamugirishije kuri terefone ati: “Ibintu biriko birahinduka ku muvuduko munini, kandi abantu bafise ubwoba ko bazokubagurwa n’igisirikare c’Ubrusiya canke n’imirwi y’abarwanyi yegukira Ukraine, hamwe n’ingabo za Ukraine zigenda zisatira”
 Aya matora acungerewe bikomeye n’ingabo z’Uburusiya canke ingabo zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya
 Uretse ko ingabo za Ukraine zibandanya zisubiza inyuma iz’Uburusiya hamwe n’izishaka kwiyonkora, haba mu buseruko canke mu bumanuko, ibitero ku bantu bafitaniye isano n’abateye igihugu bigenda vyiyongera
 Uwahoze ari umushingamateka wa Ukraine, Oleksiy Zhuravko yashimagije cane igitero c’Uburusiya, yarishwe ari kumwe n’uwundi muntu mu gitero ca misire bari kw’ihoteri mu ntara ya Kherson ku wa Mungu
 Amakuru avuga ko abanyamakuru b’Uburusiya nabo nyene bari kuri iyo hoteri barashoboye kuyanyaga ataco babaye
 Mu gisagara ca Berdyansk c’intara ya Zaporizhzhia, icegera c’umukuru w’ubutegetsi bw’iyo ntara hamwe n’umugore wiwe yari arongoye umurwi w’amatora muri ico gisagara barishwe mu gitero, indwi imwe imbere y’uko aya matora atangura
 Abanywanyi b’umuhari w’abarwanyi witwa Yellow Band  bakwiragije ibipapuro biriko amajambo atera ubwoba umuntu uwo ari we wese atora, basaba abandi kurungika amafoto n’amavidewo y’umuntu uwo ari we wese yitaba aya matora, kugira ngo bazohigwe buhongo mu nyuma, nk’uko AP ibivuga
 Iri tororokanirio ry’amakuru ryandika kandi ko aba barwanyi bakwiragije amanomero ya terefone y’abarongoye imirwi y’amatora mu ntara ya Kherson, basaba abantu babo “kubabuza amahoro”
 Ukraine yaragabishije umuntu uwo ari we wese ategura canke ashigikiye aya matora ya kamarampaka ko ashobora guhanwa n’amategeko, ikavuga ko bashobora gupfungwa gushika ku myaka 15 mu gihe bokwagirwa n’icaha
 Na Serbia isanzwe ifitaniye ubucuti bwa hafi na Moscou ikaba mbere na kimwe mu bihugu bike vya Bulaya bitafatiye ibihano Uburusiya, yatangaje ko itazokwemera ibizova muri ano matora
 Umushikiranganji wayo ajejwe imigenderanire Nikola Selakovic  avuga ko kuvyemera “vyoba biteye kubiri rwose” na poritike y’igihugu ciwe yo “kwubahiriza ubusugire n’ubwigenge hamwe 


n’ivyo yiyemeje vyo kwubahiriza imbibe z’ibindi bihugu”
 Ariko, ku gitsure c’amakungu atera ivyatsi, umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire w’Uburusiya  Sergei Lavrov, ashimangira ko aya matora ari “ukwubahiriza ishaka” ry’abanyagihugu baba muri izo ntara
 Yemeza ko mu gihe izi ntara zine zokwegukira Uburusiya zizokingirwa ku rugero rumwe n’utundi turere utwo ari two twose tw’ubutaka bwabwo, harimwo mbere no gukingirwa hakoreshejwe ibirwanisho vy’ubumara
 Amerika ivuga ko idashobora na mba kwemera ko “ubutaka bwa Ukraine bwitwa ikindi kintu atari igice ca Ukraine”
 Ku bwa Amerika, izi kamarapaka ni “amanyanga – ivyitwazo bitagira mvura mu kugerageza kwigarurira uturere twa Ukraine ku nguvu mu guhonyanga amategeko mpuzamakungu”
 Ubwongereza bwobwo bwafatiye ibihano bishasha abategetsi bakuru bakuru b’Uburusiya, muri bo harimwo abafise uruhara mu guhatira abanyagihugu muri ano matora

Umugabo yitwaje inkoho yihaye inkumbi kw’ishure riri hagati mu Burusiya, aho yarashe akica n’imiburiburi abantu 13 agakomeretsa n’abandi bashika 21, nk’uko abategetsi b’Uburusiya babitangaza
 Mu bishwe harimwo abana indwi kuri iryo shure rifise abana bababa 1000 mu gisagara ca Izhevsk
 Uwakoze iki gitero avugwa ko yaciye yirasa kandi ko icamutumye abikora kitaramenyekana
 Ibinyamakuru vyo mu Burusiya bisohoye amavidewo ku mbuga hwaniro asa n’ayerekana ubwoba mu nzu yabereyemwo ico gitero
 Imwe muri izi videwo isa n’iyerekana amaraso hasi hamwe n’igitoboro c’urusasu mu kiyo c’idirisha, abana nabo binyegeje musi y’intebe
 Abana indwi n'abantu bakuze batandatu nibo bishwe, harimwo abacungazamu babiri n'abigisha babiri  nyene, nk'uko bivugwa n'abategetsi b'Uburusiya
 Abigisha n’abanyeshure bahungishijwe bavanwa mu nyubakwa z'iryo shure
 Nyene gukora iki gitero avugwa ko yari afise inkoho ntoya zibiri, nk’uko bivugwa n’umushingamateka asubirwamwo n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Tass
 v﻿idewo yacishijwe ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi n'umrwi ujejwe amatohoza yerekana uyu nyene gukora iri bara aryamye hasi yapfuye, yambaye agapira gafise ikimenyetso c'aba - Nazi n'igitambara kimunyegeza mu maso (cagoule/balaclava)
 Uwurongoye iyi ntara yaciye atangaza ikigandaro kizorangira ku wa 29 Nyakanga (9)
 Iri shure riri hagati muri Izhevsk, igisagara gituwemwo n’abantu bababa 650
000, hafi y’inyubakwa za reta

Abari mu myiyerekano mu ntara ya Dagestan batanye mu mitwe n’igipolisi, mu gihe bariko  biyamiriza itegeko rishasha rya Moscou  rihamagarira abanyagihugu kwinjira mu gisirikare
 OVD-Info,  ishirahamwe ryigenga riharanira agateka ka zina muntu mu Burusiya, rivuga ko abarenga 100 bahagaritswe muri iyi myiyerekano ku mugwa mukuru w’iyo ntara Makhachkala
 Iri shirahamwe ryongerako y’uko rifise impungenge ku makuru avuga ko hari “abapfunzwe nabi” muri iyo ntara
 Dagestan ni intara irwiriyemwo cane cane abo mw’idini rya Islam, ikaba izwi muri kahise mu migumuko ikomeye
 Mu gihe havugwa imyiyerekano mu bisagara bikomakomeye mu gihugu cose muri ino misi ya vuba – aho abarenga 700 bahagaritswe ku wa gatandatu honyene
 Amasanamu y’abari mu myiyerekano mu ntara ya Dagestan batana mu mitwe n’abapolisi yerekana ibintu bidakunze kuba vyo guhangara abatware mu Burusiya
 Amavidewo atari make yacishijwe ku mbuga hwaniro yerekana abari mu myiyerekano bahanganye n’abapolisi n’abandi bategetsi bo mu rwego rw’umutekano mu gisagara ca Makhachkala
 OVD-Info rikavuga ko abapolisi baciye bikora kuri za nkoho zirekura imishwarara ihwamika (pistolet paralysant/stun gun) hamwe n’ubuhiri
 Muri videwo imwe, umugabo yari mu minwe y’igipolisi yerekanywe akubita imitwe umupolisi, imbere y’uko akubitwa n’abandi bapolisi bagenziwe
 Iyindi videwo yerekana umupolisi ahunga igico kinini c’abari mu myiyerekano, bamwe muri bo bagerageza kumufata no kumutega umwereka igihe yariko ariruka
 Mu bindi vyabereye ahandi, igico kinini c’abagore cahanganye n’umupolisi yari acunze ikigo c’iyandikiro ry’abinjira mu gisirikare biyamiriza n’uburakari bwinshi intambara ya Ukraine, umwe muri bo abwira uyo mupolisi ko “Uburusiya buri ku butaka bw’ikindi gihugu”
 Uyo mugore yatera induru avuga ati: "Kubera iki muriko mutwara abana bacu? Ni nde yatewe? Uburusiya bwaratewe? Ntibigeze badutera
 Ni twebwe twateye Ukraine
 Uburusiya bwateye Ukraine
 Hagarika intambara!” OVD-Info  ivuga kandi ko abanyagihugu bo mu kigwati ca Endirey bazibiye ibarabara rikuru, mu ntumbero yo kuzibira abapolisi bajejwe gushira mu ngiro iri tegeko kwinjira muri ako karere
 Amashusho yashikiriye iryo shirahamwe yerekana abapolisi bariko barasa amasasu menshi mu kirere mu kugerageza gushwiragiza abari mu myiyerekano, ariko abo banyagihugu babandanije bazibira iryo barabara
 Mu kugerageza guhoyahoya iyi migumuko, buramatari wa Dagestan Sergei Melikov yemeye ejo ku wa Mungu ko hari “amakosa yakozwe” muri iri himiriza
 Melikov yanditse kuri Telegram ati: "Naravuze kuri iki kintu imbere y’aha, ariko kandi ndabisubiramwo: iki gikorwa co kwegeranya ingabo gitegerezwa gukorwa hisunzwe intumbero yatanzwe n’umukuru w’igihugu”
 Iyi ntara izwi ko imaze gutanga ibihumbi vy’ingabo mu ntumbero yo gushigikira igitero kuri Ukraine, aho umwihwezo uherutse gukorwa n’igisata ca BBC gikoresha ikirusiya kivuga ko Dagestan imaze kubura benshi gusumba iyindi ntara iyo ari yo yose y’Uburusiya
 Urutonde rwakozwe mu ntango za kuno kwezi rwerekana abasirikare bavuye i Dagestan  n’imiburiburi 301 bamaze gupfa, abasumba aba Moscou incuro cumi
 Ibiharuro nyezina biboneka ko bisumba ibi kure cane
 Abantu barenga 2
000 baramaze guhagarikwa mu myiyerekano y’abanyagihugu kuva Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya atangaje iri tegeko rishasha ku wa gatat w’indwi iheze
 Abagabo batari bake bakiri bato bariko barondera guhunga igihugu, mu kugerageza kujabuka imbibe binjira mu bihugu bibanyi vya Finland na Georgia
 Hari kandi amakuru avuga ko mu gihugu cose abajejwe kwandika abinjira mu gisirikare bategeka abantu benshi batarabwa n’iri tegeko kwitaba ibikorwa

Abategetsi ba gisirikare ba korea y’Epfo bavuga ko Korea ya Ruguru yarashe igisasu cikekwa ko ari misire iraswa kure (missile ballistique) ku nkengera y’ibahari, igisasu ca mbere kimenyekanye ko kigeragejwe kuva mu kwa gatandatu
 Ibi bibaye inyuma y’aho hari ubwato bwa Amerika burerura indege z’intambara buherutse gushika muri korea y’Epfo mu myimenyerezo rusangi ya gisirikare, hanyuma kandi imbere y’urugendo rutegekanywa rw’icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu Kamala Harris
 Seoul (umugwa mukuru wa Korea y’Epfo) ivuga ko iraswa ry’iki gisasu ari “igikorwa c’agasomborotso gakomeye”
 Ishirahamwe ONU rirabuza Korea ya Ruguru kugerageza ibirwanisho birasa kure hamwe n’ivy’ubumara
 Igisirikare ca Korea y’Epfo kivuga ko cabonye ico gisasu kirashwe hafi y’akarere ka Taechon kari ku birometeo birenga 100 mu buraruko bwa Pyongyang, umugwa mukuru wa Korea ya Ruguru
 Kivuga ko iki gisasu cagurutse gushika ku birometero hafi 600 kigendera ku burebure bw’ibirometero 60 mu kirere
 Mw’itangazo casohoye, kivuga kiti: "Igisirikare cacu cama citeguye kandi kiriko kirakorana mu buryo bwa hafi na Amerika, mu gihe gikomeza ibikorwa vya maneko no gucungera”
 Abajejwe gucungera inkengera y’ibahari b’Ubuyapani baremeza igerageza ry’iki gisasu, bakaba basavye amato “kuguma barikanuye”
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi w’Ubuyapani Yasukazu Hamada avuga ko iki gisasu cageze ku burebure bwababa 50km mu kirere imbere y’uko kigwa mu mazi yo ku nkengera y’ubuseruko bwa Korea ya Ruguru, hanze y’igice c’inyanja cegukira Ubuyapani
 Soo Kim, umuhinga wo mw’ishirahamwe Rand Corporation, yabwiye AFP ati: "Ni uburyo bwa Korea ya Ruguru bwo kwerekana ko budakangwa n’urunani [ rwa Amerika]
 Ubwato bwa nikleyeri bwa Amerika, USS Ronald Reagan, bwageze ku kivuko c’igisgara ca Busan kiri mu bumanuko ku wa gatanu, mu myimenyerezo rusangi izobera ku nkengera ya korea y’Epfo mu buseruko
 Igisirikare kirwanira mu mazi ca Korea y’Epfo kivuga ko iyi myimenyerezo ari “ku neza y’amahoro n’umutekano ku kigwa ca Korea”
 Umupfasoni Harris yiteze kugendera Korea y’Epfo mu misi iza mu rwego rw’urugendo muri ako karere, mu bizoba bimujanye hakaba harimwo no gushingura uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubuyapani Shinzo Abe
 Icuka kuri ico kigwa ca Korea cariyongereye mu mwaka uheze, aho Pyongyang yarashe ibisasu bitari bike vya misire ziraswa kure
 Igihe ashika ku butegetsi mu kwa gatanu, umukuru w’igihugu ca Korea y’Epfo, Yoon Suk-yeol, yariyemeje gufata ingingo zitoroshe kuri Korea ya Ruguru, atangaza n’ubucuti bwa hafi na Amerika
 Mu ntango za kuno kwezi, Korea ya Ruguru yaremeje itegeko riyiha uburenganzira bwo kwiyita igihugu gitunze ibirwanisho vy’ubumara, indongozi yayo Kim Jong-un akaba yamirira kure ibiganiro bijanye no gukura ibirwanisho vy’ubumara muri ico gihugu
 N’aho yafatiwe ibihano bikomeye, Pyongyang yaragerageje ibirwanisho bitandatu vy’ubumara hagati ya 2006 na 2017

