Perezida Evariste Ndayishimiye w’Uburundi asaba ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU ko ryotahura y’uko Uburundi bwateye intambwe mu vyo umutekano kandi ko kitakiri igihugu kigoyagoya
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu nama ya bose igira 77 y’iri shirahamwe, Perezida Ndayishimiye yaragirije abakozi bamwe bamwe ba ONU baca intege iterambere igihugu kigezeko bagacuvya ibikorwa vyiwe bitwaje imvo za poritike
 Kubw’iwe, ntibigikenewe ko umurwi wa ONU ujejwe agateka ka zina muntu urungika imirwi n’intumwa zidasanzwe, reta y’Uburundi itigeze iha nirwere kuko yabagiriza ko bakorera ku makuru y’ibinyoma
 Kuva mu 2015, imigenderanire hagati ya reta y’Uburundi n’amakungu be n’amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu amwe amwe yagiye itosekara
 Bamwe mu bategetsi b’igihugu, inzego z’umutekano n’iz’igendereza, hamwe n'urwaruka rw'umugambwe CNDD-FDD uri ku butegetsi bagirizwa guhonyanga agateka ka zina muntu, ivyo reta yamye kandi ibandanya yiyamiriza
 Mw’iryo jambo, Ndayishimiye, n’aho ashimira amakungu ku kigoro yagize mu kugarukana amahoro n’umutekano mu gihugu ciwe, ntarya umunwa mu kwagiriza abakoziba ONU ko baca intege intambwe imaze gushikwako
 Ati: “Mu bihugu bimwe bimwe harimwo na rwanje, iyo intwaro rusangi uko tuyumva ishinze imizi, bamwe mu bakozi b’ishirahamwe ONU barayisibanganya mu kuvuga ko itizewe kandi ko idahuza bose mu ntumbero yo kutugumiza mu cuka kibi kidagira mvura
 “Iyo turi mu rugamba rwa misi yose rwo kurwanya ukudahana, bamwe mu bakozi ba ONU barondera gutesha agaciro ibikorwa vyacu”
 Ndayishimiye abona ko igihe kigeze ko ishirahamwe ONU ryemera intambwe igihugu ciwe “kigezeko kuva imyaka 17 iheze kandi rigatahura ko ivy’uko kikiri igihugu kigoyagoya bitagifise ikibanza mu Burundi”
 Ati: “Rero harageze (


) ko Umurwi ujejwe agateka ka zina muntu wicara hamwe n’ibihugu vyacu kugira ngo tubone kumwe ukungene poritike y’ibihugu vyacu yogenda, aho gushaka kuyobora ibikorwa vyawo iciye ku mirwi n’intumwa zidasanzwe ukwa wonyene”
 Mu gihe mu Burundi abatari bake, cane cane abatavuga rumwe n’umugambwe uri ku butegetsi, bidogera ubutungane kandi bakavuga ko agateka ka zina muntu kabandanya gahonyangwa, Perezida Ndayishimiye yabwiye abari muri iyo nama ko “ubutungane kuri bose ubu butakiri umugani" Yavuze kandi ko "n’agateka ka zina muntu, harimwo uburenganzira bwo gushikiriza akari ku mutima n’ugushikiriza amakuru, kubahirijwe ku butaka bwose bw’Uburundi”
 Kuva Uburundi bwinjiye mu ndyane za poritike mu 2015 biturutse ku ngingo y’umuhisi Perezida Petero Nkurunziza yo kwitoreza ikiringo ca gatatu, imigenderanire hagati yabwo n’ibihugu bimwe bimwe, cane cane vy’Uburengero, hamwe n’amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu amwe amwe, yaratosekaye
 Ibi vyatumye Uburundi hamwe na bamwe mu bategetsi bakuru b’igihugu bamwe bamwe bafatirwa ibihano
 Hagati aho kuva Evariste Ndayishimiye ashitse ku butegetsi inyuma y’amatora ya 2020, harabaye ukuganira n’impande zompi mu ntumbero yo gusubiza ibintu mu buryo, akaba mw’ijambo ryiwe ashima intambwe igezweko
 Ati: “Turashima kubona imigenderanire myiza (


) yari yahagaritswe n’ibihugu bimwe bimwe n’amashirahamwe amwe amwe yarasubiye kunaguka
 “Icipfuzo cacu nyamukuru ni ugukomeza imigenderanire myiza kandi ikomeye n’ibihugu hamwe n’amashiramahwe mpuzamakungu ishobora kuzana akarusho muri kazoza k’Uburundi n’ibindi bihugu”

Ishengero rya Anglican ishami ry’Ubwongereza ryabujije umukobwa w’umuhisi Desmond Tutu kuyobora ibirori vyo guhamba kubera yubakanye n’umugore nka we
 Mpho Tutu van Furth ni umupasitori mw’ishengero Anglican muri diyoseze ya Washington, akaba yari yasabwe kuyobora imisa yo guhamba uwari umuvyeyi wiwe w'ibatisimu, Martin Kenyon, ahitwa Shropshire mu Bwongereza ejo ku wa kane
 Tutu van Furth yabwiye BBC ko kumwankira “bisa n’ubugome kandi bibabaje”
 Diyoseze ya Hereford ivuga ko vyari "ibintu bitoroshe"
 Ishengero rya Anglican ishami ry’Ubwongereza (Church of England) ntiryemerera abavugabutumwa baryo ko barongorana n’abo basangiye ibitsina kuko inyigisho ritanga ari uko ukwubakana biba hagati y’umugabo n’umugore
 Hagati aho, ishengero rya Anglican rigenzi ryaryo muri Amerika, rizwi nka Église épiscopalienne des États-Unis /The Episcopal Church, riremerera abavugabutumwa baryo kwubakana n’abo basangiye ibitsina
 Itangazo rya Diyosezi ya Hanoford rivuga riti: "Hatanzwe impanuro hisunzwe aho inama y’Abepiskopi ihagaze ku bijanye n’abarongorana basangiye ibitsina”
 Uwahoze ari musenyeri wa Liverpool, Paul Bayes asanzwe ari mu bahimiriza ko ishengero rihindura aho rihagaze ku bijanye n’igitsina, avuga ko “atari vyiza kuvuga ngo ibintu ntivyoroshe”
 "Ni ngombwa ko vuba bwango kami ka muntu, umwitwarariko mu butumwa, hamwe n’urukundo, bihabwa ikibanza”
 Umuryango wa Kenyon umaze kubwirwa iyi ngingo y’Urusengero, waciye wimura igisabisho co gusezera ikivana kw’isengero St Michael ikijana kuri All Angels ahitwa Wentnor, hafi y’ikigo ca Musenyeri, ahantu hazwi cane, hafi y’aho uyu muvugabutumwa aba kugira ngo umupfasoni Tutu van Furth ashobore guhagarikira iki gisabisho avuge n’ubutumwa
 Tutu van Furth  yabwiye BBC ati: "Birababaje cane
 Vyumvikana ko ari ingingo y’abategetsi ba ruburakigongwe
" Kenyon yari incuti ya hafi cane n’uwahoze ari musenyeri mukuru muri Afrika y’Epfo umuhisi Desmond Tutu
 Tutu van Furth yategetswe guhagarika ivyo kuvuga ubutumwa nka pasitori muri Afrika y’Epfo inyuma y’aho yubakaniye n’umugore nkawe, Marceline van Furth, umwigisha wa kaminuza wo mu Buholande, mu 2015
 Se wiwe Desmond Tutu - yitavye Imana muri Kigarama (12) 2021 - yaratsindiye agashimwe kitiriwe Nobel mu 1984 kubera  uruhara yagize mu kurwanya ya ntwaro y’ivangura ya apartheid muri Afrika y’Epfo
 Nawe nyene yararwaniye uburenganzira bw’abahuza ibitsina babisangiye yongera ashigikira ukurongorana hagati y’abasangiye ibitsina
 Mu 2013 yavuze ati: Nopfuma mpeba kuja mw’ijuru ryanka abatinganyi
 Oya, novuga nti mbabarira, nshaka kuvuga ko nopfuma nja mu kindi kibanza
 “Sinosenga Imana yanka abatinganyi kandi uku niko ndavyumva cane”
 Yongeyeko ati: " Muri rino sekeza, mfise ishaka nk’iryo nari mfise mu kurwanya apartheid
 Kuri jewe, bimeze co kimwe”

Intara zine za Ukraine zigaruriwe n'Uburusiya ziri mu matora ya kamarampaka ajanye no kwemeza canke guhakana kwegukira Uburusiya
 Aya matora yiyamirijwe na Ukraine hamwe n’Uburengero, azomara imisi itanu mu gize zose – zibiri mu buseruko na zibiri mu bumanuko – zikiri mu ntambara
 Mu gihe zokwemeza ko zegukiye Uburusiya, bishobora gutuma buvuga ko ubutaka bwabwo buriko buraterwa na Ukraine ikoresheje ibirwanisho ihabwa n’uburengero
 Ibi bishobora gutuma intambara yunyuka
 Inyuma y’amezi indwi aheze kuva igitero c’Uburusiya gitanguye, Vladimir Putin ntahagaze neza
 Igitero ca Ukraine co kwivuna catumye yisubiza uturere tumwe tumwe twari twigaruriwe n’Uburusiya kuva intambara itangura ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2)
 Amatora yo kwemeza canke guhakana ko begukira Uburusiya ni imwe mu ntambwe zitatu zafashwe na Kremlin mu kugerageza gutunganya gushasha intambara
 Mu kwigarurira ibindi bice 15% vya Ukraine, Uburusiya buzoshobora kuvuga ko bwatewe n’ibirwanisho bitangwa na OTAN n’ibindi bihugu vy’Uburengero kuri Ukraine
 Mu gutumako izindi ngabo zishika 300
000, bushobora gukingira urubuga rw’intambara rufise uburebure bwa 1
000km
 Kremlin kandi yarafashe icemezo ko gutoroka, kwishikana canke gusiba ku bikorwa udafise akaruhuko muri kino gihe co kwegeranya abarwanyi, ari ivyaha bihanwa n’amategeko
 Ni ibintu bisa n’bimenyerewe kubona uyu mukuru w’igihugu yigarurira ubutaka
 Igihe ategeka ingabo kwigarurira Crimea mu 2014, yaciye akurikiza amatora yiyamirijwe ko ari amanyanga adahobora kwemerwa n’amakungu
 N’aya nyene ariyamirizwa, ibihugu bitari bike vy’Uburengero bikavuga ko atemewe n’amategeko
 Azomara imisi itanu muri zino ntara zitwarwa n’abategetsi bashigikiwe n’Uburusiya, muri Luhansk na Donetsk mu buseruko, hamwe no mu turere twigaruriwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya mu ntara za Kherson na Zaporizhzhia mu bumanuko
 Twarabonye ingene Crimea yigaruriwe n’Uburusiya mu 2014
 Mu gihe Kremlin yavuze ko 96
7% bashigikiye ko yegukira Uburusiya, icegeranyo cacoroste Umurwi w’Uburusiya ujejwe agateka ka zina muntu wavuze ko hafi 30% bonyene ari bo bagiye muri ayo matora, kandi ko ari bake bashigikiye ko yegukira Uburusiya
 Nta rusoro na rumwe rwarashwe muri Crimea, ariko muri kino gihe, aya matora ariko araba mu gihe c’intambara
 Izi ntara zine ziriko ziberamwo ano matora zimwe zarafashwe igice, mu gihe izindi zafashwe rwose
 Mu bumanuko, igisagara ca Kherson ntigitekanye muri kino gihe, ingabo z’Uburusiya zikaba zitorohewe mu guhagarika igitero gikomeye ca Ukraine co kwivuna
 Inyubakwa nkuru y’ubutegetsi yaratewe ibisasu vya misire bitari bike mu ndwi iheze
 Nta matora atekanye ashoboka, ariko abategetsi bavuga ko abantu 750
000 biyandikishije ngo batore, bakaba bategura no kwinjiza uturere tugenzurwa n’ingabo z’Uburusiya mu yindi ntara ya Ukraine, Mykolayiv, mu karere bigaruriye
 Ibinyamakuru vy’Uburusiya bivuga ko abahagarariye amatora bazoca ku nzu ku nzu bafise udusandugu tw’amatora kuva kuni uno wa gatanu gushika ku wa mbere
 Ibibanza vy’itora bizokwugururwa gusa ku musi ugira gatanu, aha hazoba ari ku wa 27 z’uku kwezi, abategetsi bakavuga ko ari kubera ibibazo vy’umutekano
 Ibibanza vy’itora biharurwa mu majana bitegekanywa kwugururwa uwo musi, aho abantu bazoshobora gutorera hanze y’intara zabo – mbere n’impunzi zibifitiye uburenganzira zikazoshobora gutorera mu turere tw’Uburusiya bwo nyene
 Hariho kandi n’umugwa mukuru wa Zaporizhzhia, ukiri neza neza mu minwe y’ingabo za Ukraine, bigasigura ko kamarampaka yo kwigarurira iyi ntara ikaba ataco isigura
 Donetsk mu buseruko yigaruriwe n’Uburusiya ku bice 60% gusa kandi iracaberamwo intambara zikomeye
 Uburusiya bugenzura Luhansk hafi yose mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko, n’aho bwatanguye gutakaza urubuga
 Ibinyamakuru vy’Uburusiya vyerekana utubendera turiko turatangwa twanditseko ngo “Uburusiya ni bwo kazoza”
 Abanyagihugu benshi b’imbere y’intambara barahunze
 Umukuru w’ubutegetsi bushigikiwe n’Uburusiya muri Donetsk, Denis Pushilin, yarategetse abanyagihugu guhunga imbere y’uko intambara itangura
 Abategetsi bashigikiwe n’Uburusiya baripfuje gukora aya matora kuva amezi atari make, ariko  ingingo yagiye gufatwa hasigaye imisi itatu ngo abe
 Nta barorerezi bigenga bazohaba
 Abenshi mu bazotora bazobikorera ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi, n’aho abategetsi bemereye abanyagihugu ko umutekano uzokwongerezwa ku bibanza vy’amatora
 Umuhanuzi wo mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi wa Ukraine Yuriy Sak yabwiye BBC ko aya matora ari impfagusa
 Ati: "Turiko turabona abanyagihugu bose bashaka kwisubirira muri Ukraine, ni co gituma hari imirwi y’abirwanira muri utwo turere”
 Kyiv ivuga ko ata kintu na kimwe kizohinduka kandi ko ingabo zayo zizobandanya urugamba rwo guhabuza utwo turere
 Umuhinga w’Umurusiya Alexander Baunov avuga ko kuvuga gusa ko uturere twigaruriwe n’Uburusiya tubwegukira ata mahirwe bifise yo guhagarika igisirikare ca Ukraine, ariko ko ari ubutumwa ku migambi bafitiye abantu bayoboye
 Hanyuma kandi Kremlin yizeye ko Uburengero buzosubiza umugongo inyuma kugira ibirwanisho vyabwo ntibizohave birasa ku butaka Moscou izoba yamaze gutangaza ko bwegukira Uburusiya
