N﻿a James FitzGerald BBC News Ibihugu vy’Uburengero biriyamiriza imigambi y’Uburusiya yo gukoresha icitwa amatora ya kamarampaka mu turere twa Ukraine turi mu minwe y’ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Aya matora yatumweko n’abategetsi bashigikiwe n’Uburusiya mu ntara zine mu ntumbero yo kuzibaza nimba zokwegukira Uburusiya
 Amerika, Ubudagi n’Ubufaransa bivuga ko bitazigera vyemera ibizova muri ano matora “y’amanyanga”
 Ishirahamwe ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe OTAN/NATO rivuga ko izi nteguro ari izo gutuma ibintu vyunyuka mu ntambara yo muri Ukraine
 Integuro zo gukora amatora azomara imisi itanu kuva ku wa gatanu, zatangajwe mu ntara za Luhansk na Donetsk ziri mu buseruko  – hamwe kandi na Zaporizhzhia na Kherson ziri mu bumanuko
 Izi ntara zine zigize ica gatanu c’ubutaka bwa Ukraine – canke akarere kangana n’igihugu ca Hongrie/ Hungary, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters
 Iciyumviro c’uko hashobora kuba amatora meza kandi yizewe mu gihe c’intambara, catewe ivyatsi ubwo nyene n’Uburengero
 Umukuru wa Reta y’Ubudagi (Chancelier/Chancellor)  Olaf Scholz yiyamirije izi nteguro z’Uburusiya z’amatora “y’irementanya”, mu gihe Perezida Emmanuel Macron w’Ubufaransa nawe yayise “amanyanga” ya demokarasi
 Macron yabwiye abanyamakuru i New York, aho asanzwe ari mu nama y’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU, ati: "Mu gihe iciyumviro ca kamarampaka ya Donbas kitoba akaga vyoba ari ibintu bitwengeje”
 Atera akamo ibihugu ataho vyegamiye guhindura ingendo ku bijanye n’iyi ntambara, akavuga ko kunuma canke kwifatanya n’umwansi ari “ikosa ridasanzwe”
 Umuhanuzi wa Amerika mu vyo umutekano, Jake Sullivan, avuga ko Amerika itazokwigera yemera aya matora, akayita ko ari “agasuzuguro ku mabwirizwa ngenderwako y’ubwigenge n’ubusugire bw’igihugu"
 Kamarampaka iyo ari yo yose itunganijwe n’ingabo zateye igihugu iteye kubiri n’amategeko mpuzamakungu kandi nta nguvu izoba ifise imbere y’amategeko, nk’uko bivugwa n’ishirahamwe ry’umutekano n’imigenderanire i Bulaya (Organisation for Security and Cooperation in Europe, OSCE), mw’itangazo ryasohoye
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine arashimira incuti zashigikiye igihugu ciwe kuri ino “nkuru iteje induru” y’Uburusiya
 Zelensky yitezwe gushikiriza ijambo Inama nkuru ya ONU akoresheje ubuhinga bwa videwo mu masaha yitereye kuri uno wa gatatu
 Hari amakuru yari ahari yavuga ko Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya na we yari gushikiriza ijambo ryiwe ejo ku wa kabiri, ibidakunze kuba - aho abantu bari biteze ko yari kuvuga ibijanye n’integuro y’aya matora, canke ku mugambi wo kwegeranya ingabo nyinshi muri Ukraine
 Ariko iri jambo ntiryigeze rishika, ahubwo abantu bakabona ko rishobora kuba ryungururijwe kuri uno  wa gatatu
 Imigambi yo gukora ano matora mu misi mike ibonwa cane nk’umugambi wa Putin wo kwihutisha igikorwa c’ukwigarurira Ukraine
 Ibi bibaye inyuma y’igitero gikomeye co kwivuna, aho Kyiv ivuga ko yabohoje ubutaka bungana na kirometero kwadarato 8000 muri kuno kwezi, ivyasubije inyuma Uburusiya
 Gukomeza igenzura ry’ubutaka bwa Ukraine bishobora guha ubushobozi Uburusiya bwo kuvuga ko ubutaka bwabwo – atari igisirikare cabwo gusa – bwatewe n’ibirwanisho vy’Uburengero mu gihe intambara zibandanya
 Aha ni kubera ibihugu bitari bike vy’uburengero bibandanya biha Ukraine ibirwanisho mu ntumbero yo kuyifasha kwivuna umwansi
 Hari ubwoba ko ibi bishobora gutuma ibintu vyunyuka muri ino ntambara imaze gusesa amaraso atari make
 Umukuru wa Komite mpuzamakungu y’ishirahamwe Croix-Rouge afise ubwoba ko iyi ntambara ishobora kuba ndende
 Avuga ku mva rusangi ziherutse gutorwa muri Ukraine, Peter Maurer yabwiye umunyamakuru Lyse Doucet wa BBC ko umwumvikano ugenda ugorana
 Abategetsi begamiye Uburusiya muri izo ntara zine za Ukraine bashigikiye aya matora ya kamarampaka
 Umukuru wa reta yashinzwe n’Uburusiya muri Luhansk, Leonid Pasechnik, avuga ati yari "indoto rusangi yacu ikaba na kazoza rusangi kacu”
 Icegera c’umukuru w’inama nkuru y’Uburusiya ijejwe umutekano, Dmitry Medvedev, avuga ko aya matora azoshobora “kurenganura igihugu” kandi ko azoba ntasubirwamwo
 Ubutegetsi bwashinzwe n’Uburusiya busanzwe bukorera muri Donetsk na Luhansk kuva 2014
 Mu buryo bwateje impari, Putin  yatangaje ko izi ntara zompi zikukiye imisi itatu imbere y’uko agomorera ingabo ziwe kuri Ukraine ku wa 24 z’ukwa kabiri uno mwaka
 Iki gitero catumye Uburusiya bwigarurira Luhansk yose mu kiringo kitari gito  - n’aho Ukraine yabohoje uturere tumwe tumwe
 Izi ngingo zo gutumako “amatora ya kamarampaka” zibukije igihe Uburusiya bwigarurira akarere ka Crimée/Crimea kari mu bumanuko mu 2014
 Naho nyene haratumweko amatora mu ntumbero yo kugerageza kwemeza ubutegetsi bwa Moscou muri ako karere, ariko nayo nyene yafashwe ko ateye kubiri n’amategeko akaba yariyamirijwe n’amakungu

Prezida wa Turkiya Recep Tayyip Erdogan yavuze ko yizeye ko umurongozi w’Uburusiya ariko ararondera guheza ingwano yatanguje muri Ukraine, kandi intambwe idasanzwe igiye guterwa
 Akurikije ibiganiro yaheruka kugirana na Vladimir Putin, Recep Tayyip Erdogan yavuze ko abona ko Putin yifuza ko ingwano yoyiheza akanya akariko kose
 Ukraine iherutse kwisubiza uturere twinshi twayo muri uku kwezi
 Umurongozi wa Turikiya yavuze ko ibintu bigoye cane ku Burusiya
 Bwana Erdogan yavuze ko yagiriraniye ibiganiro bikomeye na Putin mu nama y’abakuru b’ibihugu yabereye Uzbekstan mu ndwi iheze
 Mu kiganiro na Radiyo yo muri Amerika PBS, umurongozi wa Turkiya yavuze ko yasanze umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yari akeneye ko ingwano ihera vuba
 Mu bisanzwe ariko anyereka ugushaka ko ingwano ihera mugihe ca vuba
 Bwana Erdogan yagize ati: "Uko niko navyibajije kuko uburyo ibintu biriko biragenda muri iki gihe ni nabi cane
" Yongeye avuga ko abafashwe ingwate 200 bagiye gukabishwa n’abandi hagati y’izo mpande zose
 Nta bindi birenzaho yavuze bijanye n’abazoba bari mu banyororo bazohanahanwa
 Erdogan yagumye agerageza kuba umuhuza mugihe c’ingwano, agashira imbere intambwe yo hagati nk’uwuri mw’ishirahamwe rigwaniriza umwansi hamwe rya Bulaya na Amerika, OTAN, mu gihe yiyamiriza ibihano ibihugu vya Bulaya vyafatiye Uburusiya
 Yarafashije ONU mu guhuza impande zose kugira Ukraine isubire gushorera intete mu makungu, mu ndwi iheze kandi yariko agerageza gutanguza ibiganiro vyo guhagarika ingwano vyo kumugaragaro
 Hagati aho, nyuma y’amezi abiri ingabo z’Uburusiya zifashe akarere kose ka Luhansk ko mu buseruko, Ukraine yarisubije ibice vyako
 Umuyobozi w’intara ya Luhansk Serhiy Haidai yavuze ko inteko z’Uburusiya zavuye ku mutumba wa Bilohorivka - ariko ziriko zirakora ibishoboka vyose kugira zigume ahandi hose
 Umukuru w’igihugu Zelensky yavuze ko "abahafashe bari mu bwoba"
 Mu ntango z’uku kwezi, Erdogan yagirije ibihugu vya Bulaya gushirako amategeko asotora ku bijanye n’Uburusiya aranagabisha ko ingwano ata mahirwe y’uko yohera vuba
 Mu ndwi iheze, umurongozi w’u Burusiya yavuze ko yiteguriye kubonana na President wa Ukraine, ngo ariko Zelensky ntabikozwa
 Yabariye umushikiranganji wa mbere w’u Buhindi ko yagomba ko ingwano ihera "vuba na bwango"
 Ariko Uburusiya ntacerekezo bwatanze c’uko bwiteze  kwemera ibisabwa na Ukraine mu  kuva  hose mu ntara za Ukraine, harimwo n’izo bwafashe mu 2014
 Crimea yarigaruriwe n’Uburusiya ico gihe, kandi ubu uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu Dmitry Medvedev aheruka kuvuga ko abaharanira ukwiyonkora bashigikiwe n’Uburusiya bakwiye gutegura “kamarampaka” zo kubwomorera uturere twa Luhansk na Donetsk – ubu tuzwi nka Donbas
 Prezida Putin yaratangaje akatari gake yuko “kubohoza” intara yo muri Ukraine ya Donbas ari intumbero nyamukuru y’Uburusiya
 Bwana Medvev, ubu asigaye ari icegera c’akanama k’Uburusiya kajejwe umutekano, yaravuze ko “kamarampaka i Donbas ari kirumara”
 Abarongozi bo hasi b’intara za Luhansk na Donetsk bashizweho n’Uburusiya nabo nyene baratumyeko amatora yihuta ya kamarampaka kandi n’umuhanuzi w’umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi Oleksiy Koptyko yavuze ko vyabaye ibimenyetso vyo guhahamuka i Moscou no kugerageza gutera intege Putin mu bikorwa
 Kiretse kwifatira henshi mu hagize akarere ka Kharkiv mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko, inteko za Ukraine zaratanguje ibitero vyo kugwanya umwansi mu ntara yo mu bumanuko ya Kherson, umurongozi yashizweho n’u Burusiya abwirizwa gutevya amatora kamarampaka yo kwomeka iyo ntara ku Burusiya
 Abajijwe na PBS niba Uburusiya bushobora kwemererwa kugumya na kamwe mu turere bwafashe kuva mu kwa kabiri, canke ko ico kibazo kidashobora kuba mu masezerano y’amahoro, Erdogan yavuze ati oya, nta nkeka n’imwe
 Yongeye avuga ko ibibanza vyari vyarigaruriwe n’Uburusiya bizogarukanwa kuri Ukraine
