 Uburusiya buvuga ko buriko buriyubaka – mu gihe ingabo zabwo zikigenzura hafi ica gatanu c’igihugu cose
 Uburusiya bwateye Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma  (2) uno mwaka, zigota umugwa mukuru Kyiv
 Bwakoze ibitero kandi mu bumanuko, mu buseruko n’uburengero bw’igihugu
 Mu ntango z’ukwa kane, ingabo za Ukraine zisubije uturere tunini two mu micungararo ya Kyiv, inyuma y’aho ingabo z’Uburusiya vyankiye ko zisatira gushika ku mugwa mukuru
 Kuva ico gihe, ibikorwa vya gisirikare vy’Uburusiya vyibanze mu bumanuko, mu buseruko no mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine, maze zigarurira uturere tutari duto
 Hagati aho, ibintu vyagiye guhinduka cane mu ntango z’uku kw’icenda
 Mu gitero gikomeye co kwivuna mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko, ukraine yomoye ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Ivuga ko yabohoje ubutaka bungana na kirometero kwadarato 3000 mu micungararo y’igisagara ca Kharkiv honyene
 Muri rusangi, Ukraine ivuga ko imaze kwisubiza ubutaka busumba kirometero kwadarato 8000 bwari mu minwe y’Uburusiya muri kuno kw’icenda – ubu bukaba ari bwo butaka bunini ibohoje kuva intambara itangura
 Izyum na Kupiansk, ibisagara Ukraine ivuga ko yabohoje ku wa 10 z’uku kw’icenda, vyari ibirindiro bikomeye vy’Uburusiya mu gushikana uburyo ku ngabo zabwo
 Nico gituma iyi ari intambwe ikomeye kuri Ukraine
 Ingabo za Ukraine ziri mu ntambara yo kurondera kwiganzura umwansi mu micungararo y’intara ya Kherson mu bumanuko bw’igihugu
 Ikigo cigisha ibijanye n’intambara (Institute for the Study of War, ISW) kivuga ko ingabo za Ukraine “zakubise bikomeye” ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Justin Bronk wo mu kigo Royal United Services Institute avuga ko ibirindiro vy’ingabo z’Uburusiya muri Kharkiv “vyasenyutse rwose”
 Avuga ko, kuva zivuye muri Kyiv mu kwa kane, ubu ari bwo bwa mbere ingabo z’Uburusiya zitsinzwe bikomeye zigasubira inyuma
 Uburusiya bwaremeje ko ingabo zabwo zavuye muri Izyum na Kupiansk
 Buvuga ko zavuyeyo mu ntumbero yo “gusubira kwiyegeranya”
 Buvuga kandi ko buzobandanya bukora ibitero vya gisirikare kuri utu turere
 Igisirikare c’Uburusiya gisa n’icataye ibirwanisho n’amasasu vyinshi mu gusubira inyuma
 Ikigo ISW  kivuga ko Uburusiya bukigenzura hafi ibice 20% vya Ukraine
 Utu turere turi cane cane mu karere ka Donbas kari mu buseruko, hamwe n’akarere ko mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine, ukongerako n’akarere ka Crimée/Crimea bwigaruriye mu 2014
 Donbas ni akarere karwiriyemwo abavuga ikirusiya, mbere igihe Uburusiya bwigarurira Crimée mu 2014, inyeshamba zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya zigaruriye ibice birenga ica gatatu c’aka karere
 Bwaciye bushinga ivyitwa ama Repubulika muri ako karere
 Uturere two mu burengero, harimwo Lviv twaracucagiwe ibisasu vya misire ariko ingabo z’Uburusiya ntizahavuye ngo zigerageze gufata no kwigarurira ubutaka
 Uburusiya ntibwemera ko igitero bwakoze ari intambara, bwo bukaba bwivugira ngo buri mu “gikorwa ca gisirikare kidasanzwe” muri Ukraine
 Kremlin ivuga ko ibi bikorwa vya gisirikare bizobandanya gushika “intumbero shingiro zayo” zishitsweko
 Igihe agomora ingabo mu kwa kabiri, Perezida Vladimir Putin yavuze ko intumbero kwari “ugusambura igisirikare ca Ukraine”
 Imwe mu ntumbero kwari ugushaka kubuza ko Ukraine yijira mu runani rw’Uburengero rwo kwivunira umwansi hamwe, ruzwi nka  OTAN/NATO
 Intego ya mbere y’Uburusiya kwari ukwigarurira Ukraine bugasenyura reta yayo
 Ariko, busa n’uko bwasubije amero inyuma ubu bukaba busa n’ubushaka kwigarurira ubutaka mu buseruko n’ubumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko intumbero nyamukuru ari ukwirukana ingabo zose z’Uburusiya, “tukisubiza ubutaka bwacu bwose”
 Perezida Zelensky abandanya asaba ayandi mafaranga n’ibindi bikoresho kugira ngo ishobore kugumya uturere yabohoje twari mu minwe y’Abarusiya
 Ibirwanisho bitangwa n’ibihugu vy’Uburengero birakoreshwa cane n’ingabo za Ukraine
 Impande zompi ziratakaza, n’aho ata ruhande na rumwe rutanga ibiharuro vy’ukuri
 Ukraine ivuga ko imaze kwica ingabo z’Uburusiya zirenga 50
000, mu mpera z’uw’umunani ikaba yvuzeko yari imaze gutakaza abasirikare hafi 9000 kuva intambara itanguye
 Uburusiya ni gake butangaza ibiharu vy’ingabo bumaze gutakaza
 Ibiharuro biheruka ni ivyo mu kwa gatatu, aho bwavuga ko ingabo z’Ubrusiya 1
351 ari zo zari zimaze gupfa kuva butanguye iki gitero
 Mu kw’indwi, abategetsi ba Amerika bavuze ko abasirikare b’Abarusiya bababa 15
000 ari bo bari bamaze gupfa
 Eka n’abasivire na bo nyene barapfa
 Kuva mu ntango z’ukw’icenda, ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU ryaremeje abarenga 5700 bari bamaze gupfa
 Ariko, rivuga ko igitigiri gishobora kuba cariyongereye cane muri kino gihe

Urupfu n’ishingurwa vy’Umwamikazi w’Ubwongereza Elizabeth II vyatumye turondera kwibuka ingene abami bo mu karere - na cane cane bo mu Burundi no mu Rwanda - bashingurwa
 Mu Burundi, iyo umwami yatanze - ntibavuga ko yapfuye - haba imigirwa myinshi ijanye n’urupfu rwiwe
 Ariko abami babiri ba nyuma b’Uburundi ntibayigiriwe
 Mu Burundi intwaro y'ubwami yarangiye mu 1966 igisirikare gifashe ubutegetsi kigashinga intwaro  ya repuburika
 Umwami wa nyuma - Ntare V (Wa Gatanu) Ndizeye Charles - , nta wuzi aho yahambwe inyuma yo kwicwa mu buryo butazwi aho yari apfungiwe mw’ibohero rya Gitega mu 1972
 Se wiwe, Mwambutsa IV (Wa Kane) Bangiricenge, yahambwe muri Suisse iyo yapfiriye mu 1977
 Umwigisha w'ikirundi, amateka, n'imico kama y'abarundi,  Denis Bukuru,  avuga ko abantu basanzwe bakoresha ijambo “gutanga” bashaka kuvuga ugupfa kw’umwami,  ariko ngo umwami yashobora gupfa  mu buryo bune butandukanye, n'amajambo yo kubivuga agatandukana
 Umwigisha Denis Bukuru avuga ko mu "gucanira abana b'ingoma" aho “umwami bamwubakira ikirwa (uburiri), bakamuha ubuki bwo kunywa, bagaca bamwubakirako inzu itagira urugi, bagaca bayiturira
 Vyashika gake ariko vyarigeze kuba”
 Ibwami haba hariho umubitsi (umuntu ajejwe kubika canke kumenyesha ko hari uwapfuye)
 Umwami atanze (apfuye), umubitsi yaca afata inzira ava aho umwami yatangiye agenda arasemerera  amenyesha iyo nkuru gushika ishikire Abiru
 Abiru baba mw’ishamba ryari mu makomine ya Muruta na Kabarorore muri Kayanza y’ubu,  ari naho bajana "kubikira" (gushingura)  abami bapfuye
 Abiru bamenye inkuru baca baza gutora Ingogo (ikiziga/umurambo) y’umwami bakayijana hamwe n’ibintu vyose vyari ku kirimba aho yatangiye (inka, ibisabo, ivyimburwa biri mu bigega ), bigaherekeza ingogo
 Muri ico gihe ababa ku kirimba bose baba bahunze
 Bagaruka ari uko Abiru bamaze gutwara Ingogo y’umwami
 Nta waherekeza ingogo y’umwami
 Abiru bayitwaye aho baca hose abantu baca bahunga n’ivyabo vyose bakagaruka ar’uko Abiru barenganye
 Ikindi  kimenyetso n’uko ahahora havuga ingoma ya Karyenda ku kirimba haca havuga iyitwa Hangarizo, ikamenyesha ko habaye guhangaza (n’ukuvuga kugandarira umwami)
 Abiru bashikanye ingogo y’umwami muri iryo shamba rya Muruta/Kabarore, bayubakira urusenge, bakayishirako, bagacana akariro gake munsi yayo gushika ikiziga gisanguke
 Umwigisha Bukuru avuga ko muri iyo migirwa ibivugwa n’ivyakorwa bitandukanye
 Mu bivugwa n’uko umwami atahambwa (atashirwa mw'ivu, kuko ngo isi ntiyari gusubira kumera)
 Umuganwakazi Esther Kamatari avuga ati: “Umwami ntiyahambwa
 Yaserukira Imana, kandi ntawuhamba Imana”
 Ariko mu vyakorwa, umwigisha Denis Bukuru avuga ati: "Hasigaye amagufa gusa , Abiru barayegeranya bakayahamba, imva y’umwami ikitwa inganzo”
 Umwami yapfuye abantu bavuga ko ijuru ryakorotse
 Ubuzima bwaca bumera nk’ubuhagaze mu gihugu
 Umwigisha Denis Bukuru avuga ati: ”Nta mugabo yasubira kuryama ku buriri
 Nta mpfizi yasubira kwegera inka, baca bazitandukanya (nta nka yasubira kwima)
 "Abagore baca bakura imiringa n’ikindi cose kiranga ugushaza, n’uwo yanse kuvamwo yaca ayifukisha igishambara gisa nabi"
 "Nta muriro wasubira kwatswa mu nzu"
 Igihe co kugandara camara hagati y’indwi (iyinga) zitatu gushika ku minsi 40
 Ico kiringo carangira ku munsi umwami mushasha yaba yimye

Umugabo wo muri Hong Kong yari yagiye ku biro vy’ishami ry’ubuserukizi bw’Ubwongereza (consulat) ku wa mbere mw’ijoro mu birori vyo gusezera ubwa nyuma Umwamikazi Elizabeth II, ari kumwe n’abandi bari bagandaye, yatawe muri yompi
 Amakuru ava muri ico gihugu avuga ko uyu mugabo w’imyaka 43 yaririmvye indirimbo zitari nke akoresheje harmonica, harimwo n’izifitaniye isano n’imyiyerekano yo muri 2019, hamwe n’ururirimbo rw’igihugu rw’Ubwongereza
 Yapfunzwe hisunzwe itegeko ryo mu gihe c’ubukoloni ryerekeye kugumura igihugu, nk’uko igipolisi cabibwiye BBC
 Gushika mu gihe kitari ica kure, ni gake abashikirizamanza bakoresheje iri tegeko
 Ariko mu mezi make aheze, ibitigiri vy’abantu bakurikiranwa hisunzwe iri tegeko vyagiye vyiyongera, harimwo abahinga batanu mu kuvura ingorane zo kuvuga, aho mu ntango za kuno kwezi bagiriwe n’icaha co gukwiragiza ibitabo vy’abana “vyatera ubugumutsi”
 Amashusho yakwiragijwe cane ku mbuga hwaniro yerekana uyu mugabo ahagaze hanze y’ibi biro vy’ubuserukizi ariko aravuza ururirimbo akoresheje harmonica yiwe ruvuga ngo "Glory to Hong Kong" (mu Kirundi twosigura tuti ‘Hong Kong ininahazwe’), ururirimbo rwakoreshwa mu myiyerekano yo mu 2019 y’abaharanira intwaro rusangi
 Isinzi ry’abantu bari biyegeranije kugira ngo bakurikirane ikibiriraho ukungene ibirori vyo gushingura umwamikazi vyariko biragenda, baboneka bariko bararirimba bakurikira uwo muziki
 Amajambo y’uru ruririmbo avuga ngo “amarira ku butaka bwacu”, bakongera kandi bakavuga ngo “demokarasi n’ubwigenge”
 Igipolisi cabwiye BBC ko uyu mugabo yahagaritswe yikekwa ko “yari afise intumbero yo kugumura abanyagihugu”
 Abanyagihugu ba Hong Kong bari bamaze indwi batonze imirongo mu kiringo c’amasaha atari make mu kwibuka Umwamikazi, igitigiri gishobora kuba gifatwa ko ari co kinini c’abantu berekana urukundo bari bafitiye uyu Mwamikazi hanze y’Ubwongereza
 Iki gisagara, cahoze gitwarwa gikoloni n’Ubwongereza, casubijwe Ubushinwa mu 1997
 Mu masezerano bagiriraniye igihe Ubwongereza bushikiriza iki gisagara, Ubushinwa bwaremeye ko buzorongora Hong Kong mu ntwaro ishingiye ku cemezo c' “igihugu kimwe, intwaro zibiri”, aho iki gisagara gifise “urugero rutari ruto rw’ubwigenge, kiretse mu bijanye n’imigenderanire hamwe no kwivuna abansi” mu kiringo c’imyaka 50 iri imbere
 Ariko ibikorwa vyo guhasha imyiyerekano, itegeko Ubushinwa bwashizeho rijanye n’ibibazo vy’umutekano hamwe no kwemerera gusa “abenegihugu” ko baba aribo batwara igihugu, abatari bake babibona nko kurenga ku vyo biyemeje

Ubushikiranganji bw’Uburundi bujejwe Afrika y’Ubuseruko, Urwaruka, inkino n’imico kama "buriyamiriza ikoreshwa nabi ry’ingoma z’Uburundi" mw’isabukuru Nyege Nyege ririko ribera muri Uganda
 Amasanamu y’abavuzi b’ingoma z’Uburundi bambaye umwambaro w’ibendera ry’Uburundi bariko baravuza ingomba muri iri sabukuru yarakwiragijwe cane ku mbuga hwaniro
 Ubu bushikiranganji bushira ku rubuga rwa Twitter amasanamu yerekana abagore bariko batamba, bavuza n’ingoma z’Uburundi mu buryo butamenyerewe mu bijanye n’umurisho w’ingoma z’Uburundi
 Isabukuru ry’indirimbo n'intambo, Nyege Nyege, ririko ribera mu gisagara ca Jinja mu buseruko bwa Kampala muri Uganda kuva ku wa 16 z’uku kw’icenda, inyuma y’aho reta y’iki gihugu itangiye uruhusha ko rishobora kuba habanje kuba impari
 Isoko ryo muri ubwo bushikiranganji ryabwiye BBC ko umurwi w’aba batimbo bari muri iyi sabukuru batazwi na reta y’Uburundi kandi ko atari yo yabarungitse
 Buciye ku rubuga rwabwo rwa Twitter, ubu bushikiranganji bumenyesha ko budashobora “kwihanganira umuntu uwo ari we wese acafuza imico n’akaranga vy’Uburundi”
 Bwandika buti: “Uburundi burazi ko ingoma z’Uburundi ziriko zirakoreshwa nabi mw’isabukuru Nyege Nyene 2022 muri Uganda”
 Ingoma z’Uburundi zanditswe mu murage ndangakaranga mw’ishirahamwe UNESCO kuva mu 2014, kandi ubu bushikiranganji buvuga ko kuzikoresha binyuranyije n’amategeko bihanwa
 Si bwo bwa mbere reta y’Uburundi yiyamiriza abavuza ingoma z’Uburundi reta itabitangiye uruhusha, cane cane abarundi b’impunzi ziba hanze
 Mu 2019, reta y’Uburundi yamenyesheje ko hari abantu bashatse kwiba no kwiyitirira umurisho w’ingoma z’Uburundi mw’ihiganwa "East Africa's Got Talent" ryariko ribera i Nairobi
 Ni inyuma y’aho umurwi witwa Himbaza Club wari ugizwe ahanini n’abarundi b’impunzi baba mu Rwanda witabiriye iri higanwa wambaye impuzu reta y’Uburundi ivuga ko zitemewe mu kuvuza ingoma

Perezida Joe Biden wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yongeye kuvuga ko Amerika izotabara Taiwan mu gihe Ubushinwa bwohirahira bukayitera
 Imboneshakure CBS imubajije nimba ibi bisigura ko ingabo za Amerika zizotabara Taiwan, Perezida Biden yishuye ati: "Ego, mu gihe vyoshika hakaba igitero kitari bwigere kibaho"
 Aya majambo yacishijwe kuri iyo mboneshakure ejo ku wa Mungu, yatumye Maison Blanche/White house (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu wa Amerika) yihutira gutanga umuco, ivuga ko poritike ya Amerika itarahinduka
 Poritike ya Washington yamye igendera ku “mayeri yo kudatomora neza ibintu” - ntiyiyemeza gutabara Taiwan, ariko kandi ntihakana ko ibi bishoboka
 Taiwan ni izinga rifise ubutegetsi bwaryo riri mu buseruko bw’Ubushinwa, kandi Ubushinwa burifata nk’igice c’ubutaka bwabwo
 Kuva kera Washington yamye ari ntahomfatwa kuri iki kibazo mu bijanye n’imigenderanire yayo
 Ku ruhande rumwe, irashigikiye poritike y’Ubushinwa nk’igihugu kimwe (One-China), ishingiro ry’imigenderanire yayo na Pékin
 Muri ino poritike, Taiwan ni intara y’Ubushinwa kandi aha nta gushidikanya
 Rero Amerika ntiyemera Taiwan nk’igihugu cigenga kandi nta migenderanire ifitaniye n’iri zinga
 Ariko iracafitaniye naryo ubucuti bwa hafi mbere irarishorera n’ibirwanisho mu citwa itegeko-bwirizwa rigenga Taiwan (Taiwan Act), rivuga ko Amerika itegerezwa guha Taiwan uburyo bwo kwirwanira
 Muri iki kiganiro ca CBS citwa 60 Minutes (Iminota 60) ejo ku wa Mungu, Biden arashimangira ibi
 Ati: "Hari poritike ya One-China kandi Taiwan ni yo ifata ingingo ku bwigenge bwayo
 Twebwe ntidukokeza, ntituyihimiriza ku bijanye no kwikukira – iyi ni ingingo yabo”
 Mu kugira ico ishikirije  kuri uno wa mbere ku majambo ya Biden,  Taiwan yakirije yompi "ingingo ya Amerika yo kutadohoka ku vyo yiyemeje ku mutekano wa Taiwan"
 Taipei (umugwa mukuru wa Taiwan) ivuga ko izobandanya gutsimbataza "imigenderanire ya hafi yo gufashanya mu vya gisirikare" na Washington
 Pékin ntiragira ico ishikirije kuri ano majambo ya Biden, ariko Ubushinwa bwari buherutse kwiyamiriza amajambo nk'aya, aho Biden avuga ko azofata ingingo za gisirikare
 Muri Rusama (5), umuvugizi w'ubushikiranganji bw'imigenderanire yavuze ati:  "Taiwan ni akarere ntavogerwa k'ubutaka bw’Ubushinwa 


 Ikibazo ca Taiwan ni ikibazo kiraba Ubushinwa, kidashobora kwihanganira umunyamahanga yocivangamwo"
 Aya majambo yayashikirije mu kwishura ku vyari bihejeje kuvugwa na Biden i Tokyo mu kwa gatanu igihe yishura ngo "ego" abajijwe nimba Amerika ishobora gutabara Taiwan
 Maison Blanche yaciye yihutira  gutanga umuco, mu kuvuga ko Amerika itarava kw’izima ku vyerekeye poritike yayo
 No muri iki gihe nyene Maison Blanche yasohoye itangazo risa n’irivuguruza Biden: "Perezida aramaze kuvuga ibi imbere y’aha, harimwo n’igihe yari i Tokyo mu ntango z’uno mwaka
 Yarasiguye neza kandi ko poritike yacu ku vyerekeye Taiwan itarahinduka
 Ibi biracari ukuri”
 Ariko ubu bugize gatatu mu mwaka Perezida Biden arengeje mu majambo yiwe ufatiye aho reta ihagaze, mu kumenyesha ko hazofatwa ingingo za gisirikare – muri Gitugutu (10) umwaka uheze wa 2021, hanyuma kandi no muri Rusama (5) muri uno mwaka
 Mu ntango z’uku kwezi, Amerika yaremeye ko izoshorera Taiwan ibirwanisho vyo kwivuna bifise agaciro k’imiriyaridi 1
2 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika, ivyateye uburakari Ubushinwa
 Icuka kibi cariyongereye hagati ya Amerika n’Ubushinwa inyuma y’aho umukuru w’inama nshingamateka, Nancy Pelosi, agiriye urugendo muri Taiwan mu kwa munani rwateje impari – Biden na we nyene akaba yavuze ko "kitari iciyumviro ciza"
 Mu kwihora, Pékin yaciye ikora ibikorwa vya gisirikare vy’imisi itanu vyo kugota Taiwan
 Amerika ivuga ko bwateye ibisasu vya misire hejuru y’iri zinga, ariko Pékin ntiyavyemeje, mu gihe Taiwan nayo yavuze ko ibisasu vya misire vyarashwe n’Ubushinwa ata bwoba vyateye kuko vyarashwe hejuru cane

Na Patience Atuhaire BBC News, Kampala Inama nshingamateka ya Uganda iriko yihweza neza integuro y’itegeko ryotuma  abantu bashobora guhabwa no guterwa ingingo z’umubiri (zivuye ku wundi muntu – transplants), ivyo akaba ari ubwa mbere bizoba bibaye muri ico gihugu aho vyitezwe ko bizohindura ubuzima bw’abantu benshi barindiriye gukorwa (kubagwa)
 Annita Twongyeirwe yari yizigiye  kazoza keza
 Ariko kuva aho apimwe agatorwa indwara y’amafyigo haraheze imyaka itatu, uwo mugore w’imyaka 28 ubu arajwe ishinga ro kugirirwa dialyse canke kwibaza igikurikira
 Avuga ati “yarantwaye ubuzima”, asa n’uwaneshejwe
 Iyo umuntu ariko aragirirwa dialyse, imashini ikora ivyategerezwa gukorwa n’amafyigo, ikayungurura amaraso iyavanamwo ibidakenewe mu mu mubiri hamwe no gusohora ibitembabuzi vy’umurengera
 Kugorerwa dialyse imwe bifata amasaha hafi ane kandi ategerezwa kuja kwa muganga kabiri mu ndwi
 Hagati y’izo ncuro zibiri, umwanya munini awumara  muhira- ku ncuti – afasha mu dukorwa ashoboye, youngera agumiza ijisho ku mugwi wa Whatsapp yashinze aho abagenzi n’abandi bantu b’umutima mwiza bamuha  amafaranga y’intererano
 Avuga ati: “Nari umukobwa w’ishaka
 Nashaka gushika kure mu mashure
 Hari aho nari kuba umugenzi canke umugore w’umuntu akomeye, ivyo vyose ubu ntibigishobotse
 Yantwaye [indwara] indoto zanje zose nari mfise
“ Aronse ifyigo aterwa,  izo ndoto zishobora kugaruka
 Ariko kuja gukorwa hanze, kandi gushika ubu nta guhitamwo afise, vyomusaba ama dorari 30
000 (arenga 60
000
000 mu mafaranga y’Uburundi)- kandi ayo si benshi bashobora kuyaronka
 Amajana y’abanya-Uganda, badashobora kuronka ayo mafaranga nk’uko kwa Twongyeirwe, babayeho kuri dialyse umwanya biba bigishobotse, ariko no ku giciro cunganiwe ca $100  (200
000 mu mafaranga yUburundi) ku ndwi y’iyo dialyse n’imiti, arenga incuro zitanu amafanga umuntu yinjiza muri Uganda muri rusangi, vyumvikana ko abantu imparurwa ari bo bonyene bashobora kuyaronka
 Ibitaro bikuru vya Kirrudu ku nkengera z’umurwa mukuru, Kampala, nivyo vyonyene vya reta bikora dialyse
 Abarwayi bashika 200 nibo bitura ivyo bitaro batararanya, benshi bakaba bakora ingendo ndende kugira bashikeyo
 Ariko abo ni bake cane ugereranije n’abari mu gihugu babayeho bafise amafyigo adakora neza kandi bakeneye ubuvuzi budasanzwe
 Dr Daniel Kiggundu, umuganga umwe rudende w’umuhinga w’amafyigo kuri ivyo bitaro, yabwiye BBC ko “baca baheba imiryango yabo bakaja kuba hafi y’ibitaro
 “Uko siko bategerezwa kubaho
” Ico cumba cuzuye urwamo rw’amamashini abaforoma baguma bakurakuranya bariko baritaho abarwaye
 Bamwe mu bariko barakorerwa iyo dialyse bafise amagara make cane, baja baratwarwa n’agatiro bongera bikangura, mu gihe abandi bicaye batera inkuru
 Abavurwa bashirwa mu igwi ibiri ku munsi, umugwi umwe umwe ukaba urimwo abantu bashika 30
 Uburyo bw’ico gisata buhakwa gato kurengerwa,  bitagutuma  ata mwanya munini uboneka wo gutegura umurwayi aba ashikiriwe
 Iyo Twongyeirwe yimirije kujayo, aca  arara ku bitaro kugira ntazocererwe
 Yatanguye kumenya ko atameze neza igihe umubiri wiwe wose watangura kuvyimba mu 2018 aca amara amezi umunani ava ku bitaro aja ku bindi imbere y’uko  atorwa ico arwaye
 Ubuzima bwiwe bwaciye bucurama
 Yaciye aheba kaminuza aho yariko ariga amategeko yongera atakaza akazi yari afise
 Yaciye kandi yimuka ava iwabo mu burengero bwa Uganda aja ku murwa mukuru Kampala, kugira abe ahegereye ibitaro
 I muhira, uwo mugore avuga bukebuke aroza ivyombo neza, ku buryo, uretse pansuma ku kuboko, utomemenya ko avuye muri dialyse
 Avuga ati: "Iyo mvuye kwa muganga ndaruhuka kuko umubiri wose uba wajegenyutse
 Mu nyuma ndakora udukorwa tumwe tumwe hafi y’inzu kugira singume nicaye
” Madame  Twongyeirwe araterereza mu ncuti n’abagenzi amafaranga akenewe buri ndwi
 “Numva umenga ndi umuzigo ku bantu bamfasha kuriha dialyse
 Igihe cose umuntu abonye umuhamagaye, aba azi ko ukeneye  kumusaba amafaranga
” Yaranabajije abaryango ko hari uwokwemera kumuha ifyigo
 Avuga ko hari muvyarawe yari yemeye ariko mu nyuma arabivamwo
 N’aho uwo yamwemereye atari kubivamwo, Madame Twongyeirwe yobanje guterereza amafaranga hanyuma akarondera uruhusha rwo kwa muganga kugira  agende hanze  kwibagisha
 Hamwe iryo tegeko ryokwemezwa, imwe mu ntambamyi yoba ihavuye
