 Abashikigiye uwo mugambi bavuga ko Uganda ikeneye amategeko adasanzwe kugira hashirweho urwego rugendera ku ngingo zikomeye kugirango ntihagire ababikoresha nabi
 Iyo nteguro irimwo ishingwa ry’urutonde rw’igihugu rw’abarindiriye guhabwa ingingo hamwe no gushiraho ibigo vy’ubuhinga bwo gutera ingingo mu gihugu
 Icumba co kubaga kiza caramaze  gutegurwa mu bitaro bikuru vy’igihugu  vya Mulago ku murwa mukuru, Kampala
 Muganga Dr Fualal Jane Odubu, umukuru w’urwego rw’abaganga muri Uganda, avuga ko “bategekanya kandi gutera uduce two mu maso hamwe no gushiraho ububiko bw’urukoba/urusato ku bantu baba bahiye” Abakozi bo kwa muganga bashika 100, barimwo abaganga babaga, abaforoma hamwe n’abakurikirana ababazwe barahejeje kwiga hanze, cane cane ibijanye no gutera amafyigo
 Uretse icizere iyo nteguro ishobora kuzana, urutonde rw’ababikeneye ruzoguma ari runini, kandi bizosaba gutegerereza amafaranga
 Twongyeirwe avuga ko kwihebura bitigera bibura
 Avuga amosozi ari hafi gukoroka yagize ati: “Bagenzanje b’abarwayi ubu twaramaze kugira umuryango
 Iminsi igorana cane n’iyo ugiye kwa muganga ugasanga hari uwapfuye
 Ejo bundi twarabuze umwana w’umuhungu kandi vyaratugoye cane kuvyifatamwo”
 Ariko ku bwiwe, iryo tegeko ryohindura ibintu
 “Ryofasha abantu nkatwe kuronka ingingo
 Gutanga ifyigo n’uguha umuntu ubuzima bushasha
 “Abantu benshi baratinya amafaranga yo gufata ingendo zo kuja hanze, kandi ushobora gushikayo , hanyuma uwari agiye kuguha ingingo akabivamwo
 Urumva ko ivyo vyose bikorewe ngaha mu gihugu ingorane zogabanuka
”
Mu rukurikirane rw’amabaruwa yandikwa n’abanditsi ba Afrika, umunyamakuru wo muri Tanzania, Sammy Awami, abona ko igihugu ciwe gikwiye gufatira akarorero kuri Kenya muri poritike
 Abatanzania barihweza ibibera mu rugo rw’umubanyi wabo – Kenya – bagashima ariko kandi bakagira n’agashari, inyuma y’amatora meza aherutse, mbere muri ino ndwi hakaba harabaye ihererekanya ry’ubutegetsi, aho Perezida Uhuru Kenyatta yashikirije intahe uwahoze ari soma mbike ariko akavamwo aba umukeba wiwe, William Ruto
 Twariboneye n’amaso yacu, mu bintu ata muntu yokwibajije ko bishoboka, ingene umukuru w’umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora yerekanye ubwigenge mu bikorwa vyiwe mu gutangaza ko Ruto ari we yatsinze amatora, maze Sentare nkuru y’igihugu nayo ikavyemeza, n’aho uwari umukuru w’igihugu ico gihe, Kenyatta, yari ashigikiye umukeba wiwe, Raila Odinga
 N’aho bane mu bagize umurwi ujejwe gutegura no guhagararira amatora bivumbuye bagahakana ivyayavuyemwo, Odinga nawe akavuga ko habayemwo ubusuma burenze urugero, Sentare nkuru yaremeje ko Ruto yatsinze mw’ihiganwa ryisanzuye kandi ritagira agahonzi – icemezo Abakenya bose basa nk’abemeye
 Umugambwe uri ku butegetsi muri Tanzania, Chama Cha Mapinduzi (CCM) umaze imyaka irenga 50 ku butegetsi, nawo nyene utegerezwa kuba waratangajwe no kubona Odinga yaratsinzwe
 Imbere y’amatora ya 2015 muri Tanzania, uwari umunyamabanga ajejwe imyiyamamazo n’akarangamutima muri CCM ico gihe, Nape Nnauye, yavuze ko umugambwe wiwe wategerezwa gutsinda amatora uko vyari kugenda kwose – mbere bibaye ngombwa binjize igitsindo “hakoreshejwe ukuboko”
 Mu matora yabaye haciye imyaka itanu, umunyamabanga mukuru wa CCM ico gihe Bashiru Ally, yavuze ko vyari kuba biteye isoni mu gihe uyu mugambwe utari gukoresha ikibanza ufise ku nyungu zawo, aha akaba yashaka gufatira ku migambwe yo muri Kenya na Zambia yatakaje ubutegetsi inyuma y’umuzo w’intwaro ishingiye ku migambwe myinshi
 Ally  avuga ati: "Udashoboye gukoresha aya mahirwe, uzoba nka KANU [Kenya African National Union]
 Igihe KANU inanirwa no gukoresha aya mahirwe, ntiyigeze igaruka ku butegetsi
 Canke UNIP [United National Independence Party] yo muri Zambia
 Ufashe igihugu, koresha igihugu kugira ugume ku butegetsi”
 Muri Tanzania, wemejwe na CCM ni nk’uko uba utsinze mu kibanza c’uwuhiganwa kw’izina ryayo - rimwe na rimwe ata n’ihiganwa ribaye
 Mu matora yo mu 2020,  abatari bake mu bahiganira ibibanza mu nama nshingamateka ku ruhande rw’abatavuga rumwe na CCM barakuwe mw’ihiganwa ku mvo  bemeza ko zari ziteye amakenga, ivyatumye 18 mu  bahiganwa kw’izina rya CCM batsinda ata wubagoye
 Twatanguye gutangarira amatora yo muri Kenya imisi itari mike imbere y’umusi w’amatora
 Twaribajije nk’akarorero ingene vyashobotse ko abahiganwa ku ruhande rw’abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi batora impapuro zabo zo kwiyandikisha, bakazisubiza umurwi ujejwe amatora, mbere henshi, zikemezwa ata ngorane
 Muri Tanzania, abenshi mu bahiganwa bari gusanga ibiro vy’amatora, uretse ivyo kubagirako amakenga, vyugaye imbere y’uko baronka akaryo ko gushikiriza impapuro zabo
 Bamwe mu bahiganwa bari kwisanga amazu yabo yasambuwe na “watu wasiojulikana” (abantu batazwi), canke amaherezo yabo bakavunwa amaguru canke amaboko imbere y’uko banashika ku biro vy’umurwi ujejwe amatora
 Ingene abahiganwa muri Kenya barwanira kugira abantu benshi mu makoraniro naco cari ikintu giteye igomwe
 Imyaka ine imbere yuko haba amatora, uwari umukuru w’igihugu ico gihe, Perezida John Magufuli, yarabujije amakoraniro y’imigambwe itavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi
 Igihe bemererwa kuyakora hasigaye amayinga make ngo amatora abe, kenshi amakoraniro yarasamburwa n’abajejwe umutekano batera ubwoba bakanahagarika abanywanyi n’indongozi
 Mw’ikoraniro rimwe hari n’igiturika catewe, nk’uko vyama, n’”abantu batamenyekanye”, hagati mu bantu bakoranye
 Irindi tandukaniro riteye isoni ni ikoreshwa ry’ubuhinga bwa none
 Muri Kenya, umunyagihugu uwo ari we wese yari afise umuhora wa internet yarashobora kuvoma ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi inzandiko z’amatora ikibiriraho kugira we nyene yirabire ivyavuye mu matora
 Hano muri Tanzania, amatora hakoreshejwe ubuhinga bwa none yaratewe ivyatsi: gushika ku matora ya nyuma, iyugarwa ry’imihora ya internet ryasigura ko ata vyo guhanahana ubutumwa vyashoboka, ntibikunde gukoresha imbuga hwaniro umuntu adakoresheje uburyo bwo kuzunguruka (buzwi nka VPN), mbere no guhamagara kuri terefone bisanzwe ntivyari vyoroshe
 Uwutsinzwe nta burenganzira afise bwo kwitwara muri sentare, nk’uko Raila Odinga yabigize, tube turareka ivyo gukurikirana urubanza ikibiriraho ku mboneshakure
 Hano, ibwirizwashingiro ryacu rivuga ko ingingo y’umurwi ujejwe amatora ari ntabanduka - mbere n’amasentare makuru ntashobora kuwuvuguruza
 Ntivyatworoheye kwiyumvira ingene umukuru w’umurwi wacu ujejwe amatora – agenwa n’umukuru w’igihugu ari nawe mukuru w’umugambwe uri ku butegetsi – yoshobora kurya umutima amenyo nka mugenziwe wa Kenya, Wafula Chebukati, agatangaza ukuri ku vyavuye mu matora, n’aho vyoba bidaha intsinzi CCM n’uwiyamamaza ku giti cawo
 Twebwe Abatanzania turakunze kwishima ko turi igihugu c’amahoro kandi kirangwa n’ubumwe
 Turakunze kandi kwirata ku kungene, n’aho dufise amoko arenga 100, ibi bitaza mu matora, ibitandukanye no muri Kenya
 Igihe umuhisi Magufuli agendera Kenya ubwa mbere nk’umukuru w’igihugu, mu 2016, yaravyerekanye ku mugaragaro, mu kuvuga ati: "Ari nka hamwe Kenya yoshobora kwikuramwo ivy’amoko, coba igihugu ca mbere ciza”
 Ariko mu matora aheruka muri Kenya, ivy’amoko nta kibanza kinini vyagize kuko, mu myiyamamazo yiwe, Ruto yashize imbere ibijanye n’ubutunzi
 Rero Abatanzania bihweje urugero rwa demokarasi Kenya igezeko mu gukorera mu muco, abenshi baribaza nimba ivyo kutisunga amoko vyonyene bihagije kugira ngo twemeze ko amatora atabayemwo utunenge
 Ni vyo ko tutokwanjanjwa ku mahoro dufise, ariko ikibazo nyamukuru ni: None bidusaba kudakora (kubangamira) amatora meza kandi yisanzuye? None ntidushobora kuronka vyompi? Ni ngombwa ko kimwe kibaho ikindi ntikibeho? Ikigaragara ni uko amatora ya Kenya yemeje ivyo Abatanzania benshi bipfuza ko boronka irindi tegeko mvyeyi, canke ibwirizwashingiro
 Eka na bamwe muri twebwe batarafata ingingo kuri iki kibazo ubu barabona neza ingene ibwirizwashingiro rishasha ryoba rimeze mu kwubaka no gukomeza inzego nyamukuru, nk’umurwi ujejwe gutunganya amatora hamwe n’ubutungane, zishobora gukora ata bwoba kandi zidahengamye
 Perezida Samia Suluhu Hassan – yashitse ku butegetsi inyuma y’urupfu rwa Magufuli mu 2021 – aremera ko agiye gutorera umuti ibibazo vy’abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi basaba ko hotegurwa ibwirizwashingiro rishasha, ariko nta kimenyetso na kimwe cerekana igihe ibi bizobera
 Eka mbere nta kimenyetso na kimwe cerekana ko CCM yiteguriye gutezura imbere y’amatora ya 2015

BBC yamenye ko intumwa z’Ubushinwa zankiwe kwinjira kugira zisezere ubwa nyuma Umwamikazi Elizabeth II
 Umukuru w’inama nshingamateka y’Ubwongereza Sir Lindsay Hoyle yanse ubusabe bw’izi ntumwa bwo kwinjira mu cumba hari isandugu y'ikiziga c’Umwamikazi  mu ngoro ya Westminster,  kubera ibihano Ubushinwa bwafatiye abashingamateka batanu n'abakenguzamateka babiri, nk’uko vyanditswe ubwa mbere n’ikinyamakuru Politico
 Vyitezwe ko isandugu y'ikiziga c’Umwamikazi Elizabeth igumizwa muri ico cumba gushika umusi azoshingurirwako, bikaba bitegekanijwe ko ari ku wa mbere
 Mu mwaka uheze, Ubushinwa bwafatiye Abongereza icenda – harimwo abashingamateka indwi – ibihano vyo kutinjira mu Bushinwa n'ugubafatira amatungo kubera bagirije Pékin/Beijing guhohotera aba-Islam bo mu bwoko bw’aba Uighur
 Iki catumye umuserukizi w’Ubushinwa mu Bwongereza abuzwa kwinjira mu nama nshingamateka – ingingo ubu yafatiwe intumwa zashaka gusezera ubwa nyuma Umwamikazi Elizabeth
 Imigenderanire hagati y’Ubwongereza n’Ubushinwa isanzwe itifashe neza, iyi ngingo yo kuzibira intumwa zabwo ikaba isa n’iyije gusongera isibe
 Hagati aho, icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu c’Ubushinwa yitezwe kwitabira ibirori vyo gusezera uyu Mwamikazi ku wa mbere bizobera mu rusengero rwa Westminster Abbey , ujabutse ibarabara uva ku ngoro y'inama  nshingamateka
 Nk’uko biri mu gitabo c’amategeko agenda inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka kizwi nka Erskine May, mu 1965  Umwamikazi Elizabeth II yaremeye ko igenzurwa ry’ingoro ya Westminster ryogabanganywa hagati y’umutegetsi azwi nka Lord Great Chamberlain – asanzwe agenwa n’umwami canke umwamikazi – hamwe n’abakuru b’inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka
 Nta hantu na hamwe havugwa ibijanye no kugenzura abinjira mu bihe nk’ibi vyo gusezera ubwa nyuma umunyacubahiro, ariko iyo hageze gutanga “ubutumire ku banyacubahiro mvamahanga kugira ngo bashikirize ijambo ku nama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka mu ngoro ya Westminster”, aba batatu bategerezwa kuvyumvikanako
 Mu kw’icenda kw’umwaka uheze, Sir Lindsay n’umukuru w’inama nkenguzamateka Lord McFall babwiye uwuserukira Ubushinwa mu Bwongereza ko adashobora kuza mu nama nshingamateka kubera ibihano vya Pékin
 Ico gihe, iyi ngingo yaraneguwe na reta y’Ubushinwa ivuga ko ari “agasuzuguro n’ubuhemu”
 Ku wa kane, uyu murwi w’abashingamateka n'abakenguzamateka indwi , harimwo abashikiranganji Iain Duncan Smith na Tim Loughton bo mu mugambwe w’aba Conservateurs/Conservative, basavye bashimitse umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire gufuta ubutumire bwahawe Perezida Xi w’Ubushinwa bwo kwitaba ibirori vyo gushingura Umwamikazi
 Bavuga ko bitoba “bibereye na gato” ko reta y’Ubushinwa iserukirwa, kubera urugero rw’ihonyanga ry’agateka ka zina muntu
 Laughton yabwiye BBC ati: "Ntushobora kugiriranira imigenderanire myiza n’igihugu gikora amabi nk’ayo gikora, ataho atandukaniye n’ihonyabwoko ku ba-Uighur, ihohotera ribandanya muri Tibet kuva imyaka 60/70 iheze, co kimwe n’ivyo tubona bibandanya muri Hong Kong”
 Ibihugu bitari bike vyo mu Burengero vyarafatiye ibihano abategetsi b’Ubushinwa kubera ivyo bwagirizwa ko buhonyanga agateka ka zina muntu ku nkehwa z’aba-Uighur
 Ubushinwa bupfungiye aba-Uighur mu makambi yo mu ntara ya Xinjiang iri mu buraruko bushira uburengero, ahavugwa iyicarubozo, kubakoresha ku gahato hamwe n’ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina
 Ubushinwa burahakana ibirego vy’ihohotera, bukavuga ko aya makambi ari inyubakwa “z’inyigisho” akoreshwa mu ntumbero yo kurwanya iterabwoba
 Perezida Xi Jinping w’Ubushinwa ari ku rutonde rw’abashitsi muri ibi birori vyo gushingura Umwamikazi ariko nta wuzi ko azovyitaba
 Abategetsi b’Ubwongereza biteze ko ico gihugu ahubwo kizoserukirwa n’icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu, Wang Qishan
 Umuvugizi w’ibiro vy’umushikiranganji wa mbere avuga ko hari amasezerano asanzwe ahari ko ibihugu bifitaniye imigenderanire n’Ubwongereza bitumirwa mu birori vy’igihugu vyo gushingura abanyacubahiro

Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine yagize isanganya ry’imodoka nk’uko umuvugizi wiwe abitangaza
 Imodoka yunguruza abantu yagonganye n’imodoka y’umukuru w’igihugu n’iz’abamugendanira ku mugwa mukuru Kyiv, nk’uko Sergii Nykyforov yabitangaje mw’itangazo rito
 Ati: "Umukuru w’igihugu yapimwe n’umuganga, ntiyakomeretse cane”
 Umushoferi w’iyo modoka yagonganye n’iy’umukuru w’igihugu yaciye avurirwa aho nyene hanyuma aca arunguruzwa na rusehabaniha
 Nykyforov avuga ko inyamiramabi ziriko zirakora amatohoza ku bintu vyose bijanye n’iri sanganya
 Nta zindi nsiguro yatanze
 Ibi bibaye inyuma y’aho Perezida Zelensky, ubu afise imyaka 44, yari yagendeye igisagara giherutse kubohozwa ca Izyum, ikirindiro gikomeye co gushikana uburyo ku ngabo  kiri mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine, ejo ku wa gatatu
 Yashimiye ingabo zagize uruhara muri iki gitero co kwivuna Abarusiya banyaze ubutaka bwabo, mbere anahagarikira iduzwa ry’ibendera
 Mu misi iheze, igisirikare ca Ukraine catangaje ko cabohoje uturere tw’ubutaka bwanyazwe, maze ingabo z’Uburusiya zisubira inyuma

Ubutumire ku Bushinwa bwo kwitaba ishingurwa ry’Umwamikazi bukwiye gufutwa, bivugwa na bamwe mu bashingamateka b'aba-Tories, abanywanyi  b’umugambwe uri ku butegetsi mu Bwongereza
 Abashimgamateka bakuru   Tim Loughton na Sir Iain Duncan Smith bari mu bandikiye umushikirangani ajejwe imigenderanire kugira bamushikirize amakenga
 Bavuga ko “ari igitangaza” kubona „abateguye”  jenoside y’ubwoko bw’abanyamuke bw’aba Uyghur batumirwa
 Umukuru w’Ubushinwa Xi Jinping ari ku rutonde rw’abatumiwe kwitaba ibirori vyo gushingura ariko vyibazwa ko ashobora kutavyitaba
 Urugendo rwiwe muri Kazakhstan na Uzbekistan muri iyi ndwi rubaye urwa mbere agize hanze y’igihugu ciwe c’Ubushinwa kuva hateye ikiza ca Covid
 Ikinyamakuru The South China Morning Post  canditse ko icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu  Wang Qishan yitezwe kwitaba ivyo birori, amakuru kivuga ko kivana mu  baserukira ibihugu vyabo
 Abakuru b’ibihugu n’abandi banyacubahiro bo mu makungu, harimwo umukuru wa Amerika Joe Biden, bitezwe kuba bahari, ubutumire bukaba bwarungikiwe umukuru w’igihugu icari co cose gifitaniye imigenderanire (ya diplomasi) nabwo
 Ariko abaserukira Uburusiya na Belarus ntibatumiwe kubera igitero kuri Ukraine,  kandi nta n’umwe yatumiwe muri Myanmar kubera imigenderanire n’Ubwongereza yahagaze  kuva igisirikare gitembagaje ubutegetsi mu mwaka uheze
 Abaserukira Syria, Venezuela na Afghanistan nabo ntibari ku rutonde rw’abatumiwe, nk’uko amasoko yo muri reta yabibwiye BBC, navyo ibihuggu vya Korea ya Ruguru, Iran na Nicaragua vyatumiwe ku rwego rw’ababihagarariye gusa
 Iryo kete ku mushikiramganji ajejwe imigenderanire  James Cleverly, ryashizwe ahabona ubwa mbere n’ikinyamakuru Politico, ryashizweko umukono kandi n’umushingamateka ata mugambwe yegamiye  Lord Alton, n’umukenguzamateka wo mumugambwe wa Labor, Baroness Kennedy
 Abashize umukono kuri iryo kete bose bafatiwe ibihano n’Ubushinwa kubera beneguye ico gihugu ku mugaragaro, na cane cane kubera ingene cafashe inkehwa z’aba Islam b’aba-Uyghur
 Mu mwaka uheze , inama nshingamateka y’Ubwongereza (House of  Commons) yemeje ko  jenocide yariko irakorerwa aba-Uyghur mu Bushinwa  bw’uburaruko bushira uburengero aho abantu bagereranywa ku muriyoni urenga bapfunzwe mu makambi mu ntara ya   Xinjiang
 Ubushinwa bwarahakanye ivyo burerwa buvuga ko ayo makambi ari  ibanza vyo gutangiramwo inyigisho zo kurwanya iterabwoba
 Muri iryo kete, abo bashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka banditse bati: “ Turarajwe ishinga cane n’ukwumva ko reta y’Ubushinwa yatumiwe mu birori vy’igihugu vyo gishingura Umwamikazi ku ndwi iza, n’ubwo ibindi bihugu nk’Uburusiya, Belarus na Myanmar vyo vyakuwemwo
 “Bivanye n’uko inama nshingamateka y’Ubwomgereza yatoye yemeza ko jenoside yakozwe na reta y’Ubuhsinwa ku ba-Uyghur, n’igitangaza kuba abatunganije iyo jenoside bahabwa ikibanza icari co cose abo bandi batahawe
” Bongerako ko bitabereye na cane cane ko hari abashingamateka indwi bafatiwe ibihano, nawe uwuhagarariye Ubusihinwa akaba yarankiwe kwinjira mu ngoro ya Westminster
 Ikete ribandanya kuvuga riti: “Nizeye ko wemera ko bitabereye na gato ko hagira uwuserukira reta y’Ubushinwa yitaba ibirori bikomeye nk’ivyo gushingura Umwamikazi wacu kandi ko wotwizeza ko ubutumire buca bufutwa ubwo nyene
” Abo bashingamateka bandikiye kandi abakuru b’inama nshingamagteka na nkenguzamateka (House of Commons na House of Lords) basaba ko atawuserukira reta y’Ubushinwa yoza ku ngoro ya Westminster
 Bavuga ko ivyo bitabereye na gato
 Muri ubwo butumwa bwo kuri Twitter, uwuhagarariye Ubwongereza mu Bushinwa avuga ati : "Izina rikomeye n'icubahiro vy'umuhisi Umwamikazi wacu mu Bushinwa biragaragara uyu munsi icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu Wang Qisham yagendeye urugo rw'uwuhagarariye Ubwongereza kugira ahoze kw'izina rya prezida Xi n'Abashinwa bose
" Prezida Xi ari mu bategetsi b’isi batanze ubutumwa bwo guhoza Ubwongereza inyuma y’urupfu rw’Umwamikazi, avuga ko ariwe  mukuru wa  mbere w’Ubwami yagendeye Ubushinwa
