 Ku wa mbere icegera c’umukuru w’Ubushinwa Wang yagendeye ubuserukizi bw’Ubwongereza i Beijing ari kumwe n’uwuhagarariye Ubwongereza mu Bushinwa, Caroline Wilson, kwandika mu gitabo co guhoza  ku rupfu rw’Umwamikazi

Abakobwa babiri b’imiyabaga batowe bamanitswe ku giti mu ntara y’Ubuhindi ya Uttar Pradesh, bikikekwa ko boba baranyurujwe bagasambanywa ku nguvu
 Igipolisi kivuga ko ibi biziga vyatowe ku muhingamo w’ejo ku wa gatatu mu karere ka Lakhimpur
 Catanguye amatohoza inyuma y’uko umuryango wabo umenyeshereje ko bari banyurujwe bagasambanywa ku nguvu
 Abagabo batandatu bahagaritswe bagirizwa gufata ku nguvu no kwica
 Igipolisi kivuga ko ibi biziga vyarungitswe kugira bikorweko amatohoza
 Aba bakobwa bompi bari bafise imyaka 18 bava mu muryango w’aba Dalit, umuryango uri hasi cane mw’idini ry’aba Hindu
 N’aho ibwirizwashingiro riwukingira, uwu muryango umenyereye uhura n’ikibazo c’ikumira n’itoteza – urubanza rwo mu 2020 rwari rwerekeye umukobwa w’imyaka 19 w’umu Dalit yasambanijwe ku nguvu n’ikirwi c’inkozi z’ikibi zigaca zimugandagura mu ntara ya Uttar Pradesh rwateje uburakari igihugu cose, runerekana ingene abagore b’aba Dalit babangamiwe
 Eka n’uru nyene rwateje imyiyerekano yakozwe n’ababa mu karere hamwe n’imigambwe itavuga rumwe n’uwuri ku butegetsi
 Ibinyamakuru vy’akarere bivuga ko nyina wabo yavuze ko aba bana babiri batwawe n’abagabo bari ku mapikipiki
 Avuga ko yatewe igihe yagerageza kubatesha
 Uyu muryango uvuga ko wahavuye utangura kurondera aba bakobwa ugahava ubasanga aho bamanitswe ku giti
 Umukuru w’igipolisi c’akarere Sanjeev Suman avuga ko aba bakobwa bajanywe mu murima w’ibikaju ari naho banigiwe gushika barasandaba
 Imboneshakure NDTV isubiramwo Suman avuga ati: "Abagirizwa gukora iri bara baciye bamanika ibiziga vyabo ku giti kugira bise n’uko biyahuye”
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’ibinyamakuru vyo muri ico gihugu, igipolisi nticorohewe igihe cagera iwabo w’abo bakobwa nijoro mw’ijoro ryo ku wa gatatu, aho abanyagihugu bari bifatanije n’uwo muryango mu myiyerekano
 Igipolisi kirinubwa cane mu bwoko bw’aba Dalit
 Inyuma y’ubu bwicanyi bw’i Hathras, abategetsi bagirijwe ko ari ba sindabibazwa, ko ahubwo bakingira ubwoko bw’abakire
 Umuryango w’uyu mukobwa yagandaguwe uvuga ko yaciye aturirwa ku nguvu udahawe akaryo ko kumusezera ubwa nyuma
 Intara ya Uttar Pradesh iri mu buraruko bw’Ubuhindi niyo ya mbere ifise abantu benshi, barenga imiriyoni 200 – ikaba kandi ari yo irangwamwo ubukozi bw’ikibi bwinshi bukorerwa abagore n’aba Dalit
 Ubwicanyi buherutse gukorerwa aba bakobwa babiri bwashavuje umukuru wa reta y’intara ya Uttar Pradesh Yogi Adityanath mu gihe abatavuga rumwe nawe bamwagiriza ko arongoye reta itagira amategeko
 Akhilesh Yadav  wo mu mugambwe Samajwadi Party yanditse kuri Twitter ati:  "Muri reta ya Yogi, imihimbiri irahohotera ba nyina na bashiki babo imisi yose, birateye isoni
 Reta yategerezwa gukora amatohoza kuri iki kintu, ababikoze bagahanwa bimwe vy’akarorero”
 Umukuru w’umugambwe Mayawati Bahujan Samaj Party avuga ko inkozi z’ikibi i Uttar Pradesh ata bwoba zifise kubera reta “ishira imbere ibitari vyo”
 Priyanka Gandhi wo mu mugambwe Congress party nawe nyene yifatiye mu gahanga Adityanath, avuga ko "gushikiriza amajambo y’ibinyoma mu binyamakuru no ku mboneshakure ntaco bifasha mu mategeko”

Umucamanza yejeje umukinyi wa Manchester City, Benjamin Mendy, ku caha kimwe co gufata ku nguvu yagirizwa
 Mendy w’imyaka 28 yambitswe izera kuri sentare Chester Crown Court ku caha yagirizwa co gufata ku nguvu umugore w’imyaka 19 muhira iwe i Prestbury, Cheshire, ku wa 24 Mukakaro (7) umwaka uheze
 Uwo bagirizwa hamwe Louis Saha Matturie (atandukanye na Louis Laurent Saha yakinira Man U) w’imyaka 41 nawe nyene yejejwe ku vyaha bibiri yagirizwa vyo gufata ku nguvu uyo mugore nyene
 Hagati aho, baracaburanywa ku bindi vyaha bishingiye ku gitsina, ariko bompi bakaba bavyiyamiriza
 Matturie w’i Eccles, Salford, yejejwe kandi ikindi caha kimwe c’ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina yagirizwa ko yakoreye uyo mugore nyene
 Ejo ku wa kabiri, umucamanza Stephen Everett yategetse umurwi w’abacamanza bariko barababuranya ko babeza kuri ivyo vyaha inyuma y’aho ubushikirizamanza bunaniwe no kwerekana ivyemezo, mbere ivyemezo vy’uko ata vyaba bagirizwa bikaba vyari vyaratanzwe
 Yari yagabishije abacamanza ko batokwiteza utunyoni barondera impamvu ubushikirizamanza bwafashe ingingo yo kutabandanya barondera kubashirako ivyaha, kandi ko bobandanya bababuranisha “badahengamye” ku vyaha bitari bike bagikurikiranwako
 Imbere y’aho, igihe avuga ko yafashwe ku nguvu, abacamanza babwiwe ko hari videwo y’umugore yariko “ararangura amabanga y’abubatse” yaryohewe cane na Matturie
 Urubanza rwaciye rwunguruzwa hanyuma abacamanza basubiye gusasa, abashikirizamanza babwiye sentare ko ata vyemezo bakirondera ku vyaha bagirizwa bifatiye ku gitsina harimwo ivy’umugore w’imyaka 19
 Icaha co gufata ku nguvu Mendy yagirizwa gifitaniye isano n’ivyabaye kuri Matturie igihe umugore yavuze ko yikanguye asanga uyu mukinyi w’umupira ariko aramusambanya ku nguvu
 Mendy aracaburaywa ku vyaha bindi indwi kimwe co kugerageza gufata ku nguvu, hamwe n’ikindi kimwe c’ikubagura rishingiye ku gitsina yagirizwa ko yakoreye abagore batandatu
 Abashikirizamanza bavuga ko Mendy yari “ikiryanyi cagize ubuhizi ukwiruka inyuma y’abagore kugira kibasambaye”
 Matturie, umugenzi w’uyu mukinyi akaba ari na we amufasha, yagirizwa ko yahawe akazi ko kumuronderera abagore asambanya
 Arahakana ivyaha bitandatu vyo gufata ku nguvu yagirizwa hamwe n’ibindi bitatu vy’ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina yagirizwa ko yakoreye abagore indwi
 Aba bagabo bompi bavuga ko nimba harabaye ivyo guhuza ibitsina n’abo bagore canke abakobwa vyabaye ku mwumvikano
 Urubanza rurabandanya

Amerika ivuga ko Uburusiya bwakoresheje mu mpisho amadolari arenga imiriyoni 300 kuva mu 2014 mu ntumbero yo guhendahenda abanyaporitike mu bihugu birenga 24
 Ubushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire buvuga ibi bwishimikije isuzuma ry’igendereza ryashizwe ahabona ejo ku wa kabiri
 Umwe mu bayobozi bakuru bo mu butegetsi bwa Perezida Joe Biden avuga ati: "Twibaza ko aka ari akantu kamwe mu bintu vyinshi”
 Uburusiya ntaco burashikiriza kuri ibi
 Moscou yonyene ibandanya yagiriza Washington kwivanga mu buzima bw’ibindi bihugu
 Igendereza rya Amerika "ribona ko ibi ari ibiharuro bito kandi ko Uburusiya bushobora kuba bwararungitse amafaranga menshi mu kinyegero ku buryo bitamenyekanye”, nk’uko bivugwa n’uyu mutegetsi wo mu ntwaro ya Biden mu kiganiro kuri terefone
 Uyu mutegetsi ntiyashatse ko izina ryiwe rimenyekana
 Isuzuma ry’igendereza rya Amerika ryashizwe ahabona ntirivuga amazina y’ibihugu canke abategetsi bazwi ko baronderwa n’Uburusiya – ariko ko vyabaye ku migabane ine
 Uyu mutegetsi avuga ko igisata c’igendereza ca Amerika kiriko kiravugana n’ibihugu cacaguye kimwe kimwe ukwaco kuri ibi bivugwa vy’amafaranga yatanzwe n’Uburusiya mu mpisho
 Uyu mutegetsi avuga ko ibi bizoguma mw’ibanga
 Isoko ryo mu butegetsi ryegereye abakora aya matohoza rivuga ko Uburusiya bwakoresheje hafi $500,000 mu gushigikira umugambwe Democratic Party uri ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku vya kera bari hagati na hagati (Center-right) mu matora ya 2017 mbere, bunashigikira imigambwe canke abahiganwa muri Bosnia, Montenegro na Madagascar, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP
 Iri soko rivuga kandi ko Kremlin yakoresheje Bruxelles/Brussels nk’ikirindiro c’ibigo n’ayandi mahwaniro ashigikiye abiyamamaza bo ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku vya kera
 Amakompanyi y’ibinyoma nayo nyene avugwa ko yakoreshejwe mu guha amafaranga imigambwe y’i Bulaya be no kugura abanyaporitike mu bindi bihugu
 Abategetsi b’Uburusiya gushika ubu ntaco baravuga kuri ibi bivugwa na Amerika
 Moscou yarigeze kwagiriza igisata ca Amerika kijejwe igendereza ryo hanze (CIA) ko ryivanga mu buzima bw’ibindi bihugu, harimwo no gushigikira itembagazwa ry’ubutegetsi mu bihugu bitari bike vyo kw’isi
 Dov Levin, umushakashatsi wo kw’ishure kaminuza Carnegie Mellon University ryo muri Amerika avuga ko Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zivanze mu matora yo mu bindi bihugu incuro zirenga 80 kw’isi, hagati ya 1946 na 2000, hatarimwo ivyo gutembagaza canke kugerageza guhindura ubutegetsi
 Ejo ku wa kabiri, umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire Ned Price yavuze ko aya mafaranga yatanzwe n’Uburusiya mu kinyegero ari “uguhungabanya ubwigenge”
 Mu mwaka uheze, abategetsi bo mu gisata c’igendereza rya Amerika banditse mu cegeranyo ko Perezida Vladimir Putin yoba yaragerageje gutanga uruhusha rwo kwivanga mu matora ya 2020 muri Amerika ku nyungu z’uwahoze ari umukuru w’iki gihugu Donald Trump
 Ariko iki cegeranyo kivuga ko ata reta yo mu kindi gihugu yagize uruhara mu vyavuye mu matora
 Uburusiya buvuga ko ibi birego vyo kwivanga mu matora “bitagira ishingiro”

I﻿gisirikare ca Ukraine cemeza ko gihagaze neza ku rugamba mu ntumbero yo kwisubiza uturere cambuwe n'Uburusiya
 A﻿riko ayo makuru nta buryo bwigenga BBC ifise bwo kuyemeza mu gihe abanyamakuru batemerewe gushika ku rwasiro rw'urugamba

Na Steve Rosenberg Umwanditsi mukuru mu kirusiya, i Moscou Ni ibisanzwe ko wama wumva, mu kiganiro nyamukuru co kuri buri ndwi cerekeye amakuru ku mboneshakure y’Uburusiya, ivyo Kremlin imaze gushikako
 Ariko ikiganiro co ku wa Mungu catanguriye ku makuru adakunze gutangazwa, aho reta yemera ko ibintu bitameze neza
 Aboneka mu maso ko atamerewe neza, umunyamakuru Dmitry Kiselev yavuze ati: "Ku rubuga rw’intambara mu gikorwa kidasanzwe [muri Ukraine], iyi niyo yabaye indwi ya mbere itoroshe gushika ubu”
 "Ntivyari vyoroshe na gato cane cane ku rugamba rwa Kharkiv, aho inyuma, y’igitero c’umwansi yari yadusumbije inguvu, ingabo (z’Uburusiya) vyabaye ngombwa ko ziva mu bisagara zari zabohoje”
 Mu kibanza ca "zabohoje", fata ko ari "zigaruriye"
 Moscou yari yigaruriye utwo turere mu mezi aheze, ariko inyuma y’ibitero vyo kwivuna vyaje nk’umuravyo vyakozwe n’ingabo za Ukraine, igisirikare c’Uburusiya catakaje ubutaka butari buto mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine
 Hagati aho, gushika ubwo, ibinyamakuru vya reta y’Uburusiya bibandanya vyerekana ubutwari bw’ingabo zabwo
 Ivyabaye mu ntara ya Kharkiv ntibifatwa nk’uguhunga
 Ikinyamakuru ca reta, Rossiyskaya Gazeta, candika kiti: "Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Uburusiya burahakana ibihuha bivuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zahunze mu buryo buteye isoni, uturere twa Balakliya, Kupiansk na Izyum
 Ntibahunze
 Iyi yari integuro yari isanzwe ihari yo kwiyubaka”
 Mu kinyamakuru Moskovsky Komsomolets, umuhinga mu vya gisirikare wewe abibona ukundi: "Biramaze kugaragara ko twafashe umwansi minenerwe
 [Ingabo z’Uburusiya] zarakweze ibirenge mu gufata ingingo ari naho havuye ugutsindwa…Inkurikizi yavyo ni uko twatsinzwe hanyuma tukagerageza kuraba ko tutotakaza vyinshi mu gukurayo ingabo zacu kugira ngo ntizihave zugaranwa”
 Uku "gutsindwa" kwateye uburakari abakoresha imbuga hwaniro zegamiye reta hamwe n’imbuga ngurukanabumenyi zitanga amakuru yo “gukundisha igihugu”, aho bagiriza igisirikare ko cakoze amakosa
 Eka n’umutegetsi akomeye wa Tchétchénie /Chechnya, Ramzan Kadyrov, niko abibona
 Kadyrov agabisha ati: "Mu gihe uno musi canke ejo ata cohinduka, bizoba ngombwa ko mvugana n’abarongoye ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi be n’ubutegetsi bw’igihugu kugira ngo ndabasigurire ingene ibintu bimeze ku rubuga
 Ni ibintu dutegerezwa gukurikiranira hagufi
 Ni ibintu bitangaje”
 Haraciye amezi arenga atandatu Vladimir Putin agomoreye ingabo kuri Ukraine
 Mu misi yakurikiye, umuntu yokwibuka ingene abanyaporitike b’Uburusiya, abanyamakuru n’abihweza ibintu n’ibindi ku mboneshakure bavuga ko ico Kremlin yita “igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare” cari kurangira mu misi mike cane; ko abanyagihugu ba Ukraine bari kwakiriza yompi ingabo z’Uburusiya nk’abaje kubabohora, kandi ko reta ya Ukraine yari gutembagara mu kanya isase
 Siko vyagenze
 Ahubwo, mu kiringo kirenga amezi atandatu, igisirikare c’Uburusiya kigenda gitakaza urubuga
 Rero, ng’iki ikibazo nyamukuru: none ibi birashobora kugira ingaruka za poritike kuri Vladimir Putin? Ivyo ari vyo vyose, mu kiringo kirenga imyaka 20, Putin yarabaye rurangiranwa imbere y’incabwenge z’Uburusiya, ko yamye atsinda urugamba; ko yamye aca mu bihe bigoye cane akabitsinda; mu majambo make ko adashobora gutsindwa
 Nkunze kumufata nk’umurusiya karuhariwe yamenyekanye nk’umuhinga mu gukwepa, Harry Houdini
 Iyo hari ikintu ico ari co cose kimuzibira canke kimugoye, Putin yamye, igihe cose, abicamwo
 Ibintu vyagiye guhinduka kuwa 24 Ruhuhuma (2)
 Amezi atandatu aheze yerekana ko Perezida Putin yakoze ibiharuro atari vyo na gato ku ngingo yiwe yo gutera Ukraine
 Uretse ko yananiwe no gushika ku ntsinzi vuba bwango, Uburusiya bwinjijwe mu ntambara ndende, kandi iriko iratikiriramwo abatari bake, mbere ikaba imaze gutsindwa mu buryo buteye isoni
 Iyo ibintu bihindutse ku mutegetsi asanzwe azwi ko adatsindwa, bishobora kumuzanira ingorane
 Kahise k’Uburusiya kazotegerezwa kwigisha Vladimir Putin
 Abakuru b’ibihugu b’Uburusiya bose barwanye intambara bakazitsindwa muri kahise ntibigeze barangiza neza
 Igihe Uburusiya butsindwa n’Ubuyapani, vyavuyemwo impinduka z’Ubutegetsi mu Burusiya (Révolution russe/Russian Revolution) mu 1905
 Amakosa ya gisirikare mu gihe c’intambara ya mbere y’isi yose yatumye haba impinduka z’Ubutegetsi mu 2017 zavuyemwo isenyuka z’ubutegetsi bw’igi Tsar
 Hagati aho, Perezida Putin nta mugambi afise wo kurangiza intambara atsinzwe
 Ejo ku wa mbere, umuvugizi wiwe Dmitry Peskov yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: “Igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare [c’Uburusiya] kirabandanya kandi kizobandanya gushika aho intumbero zose twihaye kuva mu ntango zizoshikwako”
 Ibi bidushikana ku kindi kibazo gikomeye: none Putin azoca akora iki? Ntivyoroshe kuronka umuntu ashobora kuba azi ivyo Vladimir Putin yibaza canke ategura
 Vyinshi vyoba biva ku kuri kw’amakuru ahabwa n’abarongoye igisirikare n’ibisata vy’igendereza
 Ariko aha hari ibintu bibiri tuzi: ni gake umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yemera ko yakoze amakosa
 Kandi ni gake yemera guhinduka
 Dufatiye ku vyo ibinyamakuru vya reta bitangaza, turamaze kubona ibimenyetso vyerekana ko ugutsindwa ku rugamba kuriko kwegekwa ku mfashanyo Ukraine ihabwa n’Uburengero
 Imboneshakure ya Reta y’Uburusiya itangaza iti: "Ku mfashanyo ya OTAN/NATO, Kyiv yatanguje igitero co kwivuna”
 Hari ikibazo kitoroshe kimaze amezi atari make mu mitwe y’abantu: mu gihe yonanirwa no gutsinda intambara akoresheje ibirwanisho bisanzwe, Perezida Putin azohava yikora ku birwanisho ruhonyanganda vy’ubumara? Mu misi mike gusa iheze, umukuru wa gisirikare wa Ukraine, Valeriy Zaluzhnyi, yagabishije ati: "Hari ubwoba ko ingabo z’Uburusiya, mu bihe kanaka, zishobora gukoresha ibirwanisho vy’ubumara”
 Gushika ubu, nta bimenyetso vyerekana ko Kremlin ifise ubwoba
 Imboneshakure y’Uburusiya yerekana icizere
 Ivuga ko ibisasu vya misire biherutse guterwa ku bigo vy’amasoko ntanganguvu ya Ukraine ari “impinduka zikomeye mu gikorwa kidasanzwe”
 Naho ku muyobozi wa Kremlin, ku wa gatandatu uheze - ubwo amakuru yaza avuye muri Ukraine avuga ko Uburusiya bwatakaje ubutaka – asubiye i Moscou, Vladimir Putin yari yisanzuye igihe yariko yugurura urugori rushasha, runini cane ku mugabane wose wa Bulaya
 Perezida asa n’uwucizeye ko igikorwa ciwe kidasanzwe kizomugendera neza

Ihagarikwa ry'abiyamiriza intwaro ya cami mu Bwongereza inyuma y'urupfu rw'Umwamikazi "riteye impungenge", nk'uko abaharanira ubwisanzure bwo gushikiriza ijambo babivuga
 Igipolisi muri Ecosse/Scotland cahagaritse abantu babiri muri ino misi ya vuba bagirizwa guhungabanya amahoro, uwundi nawe akaba yarahagaritswe hanyuma ararekurwa i Oxford
 Iri hagarikwa ryabaye mu gihe hari ibirori vyo kwibuka urupfu rw'Umwamikazi n'iyimikwa rya Charles III nk'Umwami mushasha w'Ubwongereza
 Abaharanira ubwisanzure bwo gushikiriza ijambo bavuga ko uburenganzira bwo kuja mu myiyerekano ari ngombwa kandi ko butegerezwa gukingirwa
 Ku wa Mungu, umugore w'imyaka 22 yaragirijwe guhungabanya amahoro inyuma yo guhagarikwa igihe hari ibirori vyo kwimika Umwami hanze y'Urusengero rukuru rwitiriwe Umweranda Giles i Edinburgh
 Mu nyuma yahavuye arekurwa ariko akazorenguka muri Sentare ya Edinburgh mu misi iri imbere
 Kuri uwo musi nyene, Symon Hill w'imyaka 45 yarahagaritswe yiketswe guhungabanya umutekano igihe ashiriye ijwi hejuru ngo "Ni nde yamutoye?" mu kindi gihe Umwami yariko ashikiriza ijambo i Oxford
 Igipolisi ca Thames Valley cavuze ko yahavuye arekurwa kandi ko yariko afasha abapolisi "ku gushaka kwiwe"
 Ku wa mbere, umugabo w'imyaka 22 yarahagaritswe yagirizwa guhungabanya amahoro inyuma yo kwikekwa ko yaciriyemwo umuganwa Andrew mu gihe hari urugendo rwa cami i Edinburgh
 Ruth Smeeth, umuyobozi nshingwabikorwa w'ishirahamwe Index on Censorship, avuga ko iri hagarikwa "riteye impungenge", akongerako ati: "Ni ngombwa ko tumera magabo kugira ngo ibi birori ntibikoreshwe, haba giturumbuka canke vyateguwe, mu guhonyanga mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose uburenganzira bwo gushikiriza ijambo abanyagihugu basanzwe bafise"
 Silkie Carlo, umukuru w'ishirahamwe Big Brother Watch, avuga ko igipolisi gifise "igikorwa co gukingira uburenganzira bw'abanyagihugu bwo kugira imyiyerekano, nk'uko kandi bafise igikorwa co kworohereza uburenganzira bw'abanyagihugu bwo kwerekana ko bamushigikiye, akababaro canke kumwunamira"
 Jodie Beck, ajejwe imigambi n'isekeza mw'ishirahamwe Liberty, avuga ko "biteye impungenge nyinshi kubona igipolisi gikoresha inguvu zabo nyinshi bafise mu buryo burenze urugero"
 Avuga ati: "Ukugira imyiyerekano si ikintu gitangwa na reta, ni uburenganzira shingiro"
 Ku wa mbere kandi, umwe yari mu myiyerekano afise icapa canditseko ngo "Si umwami wanje" hanze y'ingoro y'inama nshingamateka imbere y'uko umwami ashika kuri  Westminster Hall yarirukanywe n'igipolisi
 Igipolisi kivuga ko umunyagihugu yasabwe kwigira kure y'ikirimba ca Westminster "mu ntumbero yo kworohereza imodoka kwinjira no gusohoka kumabariyeri" ariko ko atahagaritswe canke no ategekwe kuva mu micungararo
 Igipolisi kiragira kandi ico gishikirije kuri videwo izunguruka ku mbuga hwaniro aho umupolisi yumvikana abaza ivyerekeye umugabo yari yitwaje urukaratasi ruri gusa ashaka kwandikako ngo "Si Umwami wanje"
 Uyu mupolisi - avugwa ko yari yaje avuye ahandi kugira afashe igipolisi cari kihari - yumvikana avuga ko ubwo butumwa "bwari kubabaza abantu"
 Itangazo ry'uwungirije icegera ca Komiseri Stuart Cundy rivuga riti: "Abanyagihugu bafise uburenganzira bwo kugira imyiyerekano kandi twarabisiguriye abapolisi bose bari mu gikorwa kidasanzwe kihari ubu"
 Abasirikare hafi 1500 barakorana n'abapolisi hamwe n'abakozi b'abasivire mu ntumbero yo gucungera isinzi ry'abantu ryitezwe i Londres mu ndwi iza
 Umukuru w'igipolisi Sir Mark Rowley avuga ko igipolisi cahuye "n’ikibazo gikomeye"
 Ati: "Ibirori bizogenda neza, ariko tuzotegekanya ibihumbi vy'abapolisi kubera urugero rw'umutekano rukenewe hamwe n'amamiriyoni y'abantu bashaka kumwunamira"
 Umuvugizi w'umushikiranganji wa mbere ntiyashatse kugira ico ashikirije ku bantu bahagaritswe, ariko avuga ati: "Mu bisanzwe, biragaragara ko iki ari igihe c'ikigandaro mu gihugu cose kuri benshi, igitigiri kinini, kinini mu gihugu
 "Ariko uburenganzira shingiro bwo kugira imyiyerekano buguma ari inkingi ya demokarasi yacu"

