I﻿gisirikare ca Ukraine cemeza ko gihagaze neza ku rugamba mu ntumbero yo kwisubiza uturere cambuwe n'Uburusiya
 A﻿riko ayo makuru nta buryo bwigenga BBC ifise bwo kuyemeza mu gihe abanyamakuru batemerewe gushika ku rwasiro rw'urugamba

Ingabo za Ukraine zaruta iz’Uburusiya ku rugero rwa munani kuri umwe mu gitero co mu ndwi iheze co kugaruza ibice vyinshi vy’intara ya Kharkiv, nk’uko bivugwa n’umwe mu barusiya bakomeye barangurira imirimo muri ico gice
 Vitaly Ganchev yabwiye television y’Uburusiya ko ingabo za Ukraine zafashe ibigwati mu buraruko mbere ziranashika ku rubibe bihana n’Uburusiya
 Ukraine ivuga ko yagaruje akarere karenga kirometero kwadarato 1
158 (1
157km2) mu gishobora kuba ariyo ntambwe ya mbere ikomeye cane muri iyo ntambara imaze amezi atandatu
 BBC ntishobora guhinyuza ivyo biharuro
 Igisirikare ca Ukraine kivuga ko cagaruje ibigwati 20 mu masaha 24 aheze yonyene, mu gitero cayo kibandanya co kugaruza intara zari zafashwe n’Uburusiya
 Yavuze kandi ko ingabo zaco zagaruje akarere kangana hafi 500km2 mu ntara y’amajepfo ya Kherson
 Abategetsi mu bushikiranganji bw’Ubwongereza bujejwe imigenderanire bavuga ko ivyo ingabo za Ukraine zashitseko bizogira ingaruka zikomeye ku buryo Uburusiya buriko buragwana iyo ntambara muri rusangi
 Ariko umuvugizi wa Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu mu Burusiya) Dmitry Peskov ntivyamuciye intege, avuga ko ibikorwa vya gisirikare muri Ukraine bizokomeza ”gushika  imirimo yose yategekanijwe mu ntango” irangutse
 Yongeye avuga ko prezida Vladmir Putin aguma ahabwa amakuru agezweho y’ibiriko biraba
 Uburusiya bwavuze ko ingabo zabwo ziriko ziragaba ibitero vy’indege muri utwo turere Ukraine iherutse kugaruza
 Aho harimwo Izyum na Kupiansk Ukraine yisubije ku wa gatandatu
 Uburusiya bwemeye ko ingabo zabwo ”muri ivyo bisagara kugirango zisubire ”kwisuganya”
 Uburusiya bwagirijwe kuba buriko buratumbereza ku bikorwa remezo bisanzwe (vy’igi-sivire) mu kwihora ku kubiriko biraba ku rugamba
 Urutavanako rw’ibitero vy’indege ku wa gatandatu rwatumye amatara acika muri ako karere
 Ico kizime cakoze ku bantu baharurwa muri za miriyoni mu ntara ya Kharkiv na Donetsk
 Ihor Terekhov, umukuru w’igisagara ca Kharkiv, yavuze ko ari igikorwa c’ubukozi bw’ikibi n’ubugome nk’inzira yo kwihora kubera ivyo igisirikare ca Ukraine giherutse gushikako
 Umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi, Oleksii Reznikov, yavuze ko icihutirwa ubu ari ukugumya utwo turere twagarujwe mu ndwi imwe mu ntara ya Kharkiv
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya zisa n’izataye ibikoresho vya gisirikare n’ibigwanisho vyinshi igihe zariko zirava mu turere zari zafashe mu ndwi za mbere z’iyo ntambara
 Hari ivyegeranyo bivuga ko uruganda rw’Uburusiya rukora ibiduga ntamenwa vyo ku rugamba ubu ruriko rurakora amasaha 24 kuri 24 kuva ibintu bihindutse ku rugamba
 Abakozi mu ruganda rwa Uralvagonzavod muri Nizhny Tagil, uruganda rwa mbere runini rw’Uburusiya rukora ibiduga ntamenwa, bivugwa ko batemerewe kuja mu kiruhuko kubera ”ibikenewe gukorwa”

Urugendo rwa nyuma kandi rubabaje rw’Umwamikazi  Queen Elizabeth II w’ubwongereza rwatanguye kuri uno wa Mungu, ikiziga ciwe kikaba kivanywe i Balmoral kijanwa ku kirimba c’umwami ca Holyroodhouse muri  Edinburgh
 Ibihumbi n’ibihumbi baratonze ku mabarabara mu kwunamira ubwa nyuma umwamikazi
 Iyi niyo ntambwe ya mbere y’ibikorwa vyo kumushingura vyitezwe mu ndwi iza i Londres/London
 Ikiziga kigenda bukebuka n’imodoka gushika Edinburgh uburebure bw’ibirometero 280
 Gicishwa mu bibanza bitandukanye kuva Aberdeen, Dundee, na Perth, uru rukaba ari urugendo ruza kumara amasaha atandatu
 Kiza gushikanwa i Holyroodhouse – ingoro y’Umwami w’Ubwongereza ku mugwa mukuru wa Ecosse/Scotland – kikaza gushirwa mu cumba kidasanzwe
 Ku muhingamo w’ejo ku wa mbere, hazoba ikigandaro mw’Isengero nkuru yitiriwe Umweranda Giles, kizokwitabirwa n’umuryango w’i bwami
 Isandugu izohamara amasaha 24, kugira ngo abantu bashobore kumwunamira ubwa nyuma
 Umusi uzokurikira Umuganwakazi Anne azoherekeza ikiziga ca nyina wiwe mu gihe kizoba gitwawe n’indege i Londres
  Isandugu y’ikiziga c’Umwamikazi kizovanwa ku kibuga c’indege ca Edinburgh ijanwe i Buckingham n’indege gigishijwe ku kibuga c’indege ca RAF Northolt
 Ku wa gatatu, ikiziga c’Umwamikazi kizojanwa mu ngoro ya Westminster (Westminster Hall) inyuma gatoya y’isaha umunani z’umuhingamo, urugeno ruzomara iminota yaba 40, abanyagihugu bakazoronka akaryo ko kumwunamira muri uru rugendo
 Niho kizoguma imbere yo gushingurwa
 Ibirori vyo gushingura umwamikazi Elizabeth bizoba ku wa mbere igenekerezo rya 19 Nyakanga (9), 2022 mw’isengero Westminster Abbey, nk’uko itangazo ryasohowe n’ikirimba ca Buckingham ribivuga
 Uru rusengero ni urusengero rudasanzwe kuko niho abami n’abamikazi bimikirwa, harimwo n’uyu Mwamikazi nyene mu 1953, rukaba ari narwo rwabereyemwo ubugeni bwiwe n’Umuganwa Philip mu 1947
 Nta birori vyo gufuba umwami vyari bwigere bibera muri uru rusengero kuva mu kinjana ca 18, n’aho ibirori vyo gushingura nyina w’uyu Mwamikazi ari ho vyabereye mu 2002
 Abakuru b’ibihugu bavuye mu bihugu bitandukanye vy’isi bazofata urugendo bagiye kwifatanya n’umuryango w’I bwami kwibuka ubuzima bw’umwamikazi n’ibikorwa vyiwe
 Abanyaporitike bakomakomeye n’abahoze ari abashikiranganji ba mbere b’Ubwongereza nabo nyene bazokwitabira ibi birori
 Ibirori bizotangurwa no kuvana isandugu y’ikiziga c’umwamikazi mu cumba ca Westminster itwarwe mu Rusengero rwa Westminster mu modoka y’igisata ca gisirikare kirwanira mu mazi
 Inyuma y’ibi birori, ikiziga kizovanwa i Westminster Abbey kijanwe ahitwa Wellington Arch, ari naho kizovanwa kigatwarwa gushingurwa i Windsor

Ingabo z’Uburusiya zavuye mu bisagara bikomeye mu buseruko bwa Ukraine, mu gihe Ukraine iriko itera intambwe mu bitero vyayo vyo kwivuna umwansi
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine bavuga ko ejo ku wa gatandatu ingabo zayo zinjiye muri Kupiansk, igisagara ngirakamaro kuko ari co cacishwamwo uburyo bw’ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Uburusiya buvuga ko ingabo zabwo kandi zavuye mu gisagara ca Izyum kugira ngo “zisubire zisuganye”
 Ubu bushikiranganji nyene buremeza kandi ko ingazo z’Uburusiya zavuye mu gisagara kigira gatatu ca Balaklyia  mu ntumbero yo “kwongereza inguvu” ku rugamba rwa Donetsk
 Izi ntambwe zatewe n’ingabo za Ukraine – mu gihe zorama – zoba ari zo za mbere zikomeye kuva ingabo z’Uburusiya zomotse zikava mu micungararo y’umugwa mukuru Kyiv mu kwa kane
 Mw’ijambo yaraye ashikirije mw’ijoro ry’ejo ku wa gatandatu, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky avuga ko ubu Ukraine, kuva itanguye ibitero vyo kwivuna mu ntango z’uku kwezi, imaze kubohoza ubutaka bufise uburinganire bwa kirometero kwadarato 2000 bwari bwigaruriwe n’Uburusiya
 Aya majambo asobora kuba asigura ko igice c’ubu butaka cabohojwe mu masaha 48 yonyene aheze  - kuko ari incuro zibiri ku butaka Zelensky yavuze ko bwari bumaze kwisubizwa igihe ashikiriza ijambo ku mugoroba wo ku wa kane
 Kubona Uburusiya bwemeje ko bwavuye muri Izyum ni ikintu gikomeye kuko cari ikirindiro ca gisirikare ngirakamaro kuri Moscou
 Itangazo ry’Uburusiya rivuga riti: "Harateguwe igikorwa c'iminsi itatu co kugabanya no kwimura ingabo ziri Izyum-Balakliya ku butaka bwa Repubulika ya Donetsk
" "Mu ntumbero yo gukingira ingabo z’Uburusiya, umwansi yabanje guhashwa bikomeye”
 Inyuma y’aho gato, umukuru w’uturere tw’intara ya Kharkiv tugenzurwa n’Uburusiya yategetse abanyagihugu batwo ko bahungira mu Burusiya “kugira bakize igufa”, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru rya reta y’Uburusiya, Tass
 Buramatari w’intara ya Belgorod mu Burusiya ihana urubibe na Kharkiv avuga ko abantu batonze imirongo barondera kujabuka umupaka bazoshobora kugaburirwa, bahabwe ibibafasha mu mbeho bongere bavurwe
 Izi ntambwe zizofatwa nk’ikimenyetso c’uko igisirikare ca Ukraine gifise ubushobozi bwo kwisubiza ubutaka bwigaruriwe n’Uburusiya, kandi zikaba ari kirumara mu gihe Kyiv ibandanya isaba incuti zayo zo mu Burengero ko zobandanya ziyifata mu mugongo mu buryo bwa gisirikare
 Umwihwezo wa Orla Guerin, umunyamakuru akorera hagati muri Ukraine Umuvuduko w’uru rugamba rwo kwikurako umwansi ntiwatangaje Abarusiya gusa, watangaje kandi na bamwe mu banya-Ukraine
 Ntivyoroshe ko abanyagihugu baronka amakuru agezweho
 Ubu Abarusiya bamaze gutakaza ibirindiro bibiri nyamukuru bacishako ibikoresho vyabo – ibisagara bicamwo gari ya moshi vya Izyum na Kupiansk
 Ku gisirikare  c’Uburusiya uku ni ugutsindwa kandi ni akamaramaza kuri Perezida Putin imbere y’abanyagihugu
 Ntidushobora gushika ku rugamba
 Abanyamakuru barabujijwe gushikayo
 Ukraine yariyemeje kugenzura amakuru ajanye n’intambara
 Ariko amashusho atari make ariko arazunguruka ku mbuga hwaniro yerekana ingabo za Ukraine ziduza ibendera mu turere ziherutse kubohoza
 Ibi vyose bitera intege Ukraine kandi bigahumuriza incuti zayo zo mu Burengero
 Uburusiya buracagenzura hafi ica gatanu c’igihugu kandi ni bake bashobora kwiyumvira ko intambara ishobora kurangira vuba
 Ariko abanya-Ukraine ubu barerekanye ko ku rugamba bashobora kunesha Abarusiya, atari kubarusha amayeri vyonyene
 Nk’uko umwe mubahinga ba gisirikare abivuga, nibwo bwa mbere kuva ku Ntambara ya Kabiri y’isi yose Uburusiya butakaje imirwi y’abasirikare yose
 Imbere y’aha, abategetsi bo mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna umwansi b’Ubwongereza bari bavuze ko Ukraine yateye intambwe gushika ku birometero 50 mu karere kahoze kigaruriwe n’Uburusiya
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi w’Ubwongereza avuga ati: "Ingabo z’Uburusiya zisa n’uko zatewe giturumbuka
 Aka karere ntikari gacungerewe cane kandi ingabo za Ukraine zarigaruriye canke zirakikuje ibisagara bitari bike”
 Ukraine  yatanguje ibitero vyo kwivuna mu buseruko mu ntango z’ino ndwi, mu gihe amakungu yari yiteze ko itera intambwe hafi y’igisagara ca Kherson kiri mu bumanuko
 Abahinga bemeza ko Uburusiya bwatwaye zimwe mu ngabo zabwo karuhariwe gucungera iki gisagara
 Ariko hampande y’itambwe iriko iratera mu buseruko, Ukraine iriko iratera ija imbere mu bumanuko nk’uko umutegetsi umwe abivuga
 Nataliya Gumenyuk, umuvugizi w’ibiro vya gisirikare vya Ukraine mu bumanuko, avuga ko bateye intambwe “hagati y’ibirometero bibiri na mirongo” muri ico gice
 Ariko ingabo z’Uburusiya zirwanira mu bumanuko zivugwa ko zubatse ibirindiro bikomeye, kandi ko ingabo za Ukraine zivunwa bikomeye kuva uru rugamba rutanguye
 Hanyuma kandi no muri Kharkiv na yo nyene, umuntu umwe yarishwe amazu atari make arononekara ejo ku wa gatandatu igihe igisasu ca muzinga c’Uburusiya caterwa muri ico gisagara, nk’uko bivugwa n’abategetsi
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine berekanye isanamu ku mbuga hwaniro isa n’iyerekana ingabo za Ukraine zidugije ibendera ry’igihugu cabo imbere y’ibiro bikuru vy’igisagara ca Kupiansk, zihagaze kw’ibendera ry’Uburusiya
 Ku wa gatanu, Perezida Zelensky yavuze ko ingabo ziwe zariko “zigarurira bukebuke uturere dushasha” zongera “zisubizayo ibendera rya Ukraine zikingira kandi abanyagihugu bacu bose”
 Yavuze kandi ko abapolisi bariko barasubizwa mu turere twabohojwe, agasaba abanyagihugu kubaha amakuru baramutse biketse ivyaha vyo mu ntambara vyakozwe n’Abarusiya
 Ateye aka kamo inyuma y’icegeranyo c’umurwi w’abahinga ba ONU muri Ukraine aho bavuga ko begeranije “amakuru atari make y’ihohotera ry’abapfungwa b’intambara” vyakozwe n’ingabo za Moscou
 Iki cegeranyo kandi kiragiriza ingabo za Ukraine ko “zakoreye iyicarubozo zongera zihohotera impfungwa z’intambara”

