 Bari kumwe n’abagore babo, Catherine na Meghan, baramukanije n’abantu i Windsor, mu buryo butari bwitezwe mu ndwi iheze, igihe aba basamuragwa basubira mu Bwongereza
 Ico gihe havugwa indyane n’ukudacana uwaka hagati y’imiryango ya William na Harry 
