 Bisa n’uko hari haciye igihe kirekire, ariko inyuma y’aho Umwamikazi, inakuru wabo, vyankiye, igihugu cose kiriko kibaza amakuru y’amagara yiwe, aba bavukanyi vyabaye ngombwa ko bompi bafata ingendo bakaja i Balmoral aho yari arwariye
