  William na Harry bari bamaze kuba mu bihe bigoye cane bakiri abana, igihe nyina wabo, Umuganwakazi Diana apfa ahitanywe n’isanganya mu 1997
 Ku banyagihugu bari babirindiranye igishika, mu ntumbero yo kwerekana ko bifatanije umubabaro n’umuryango w’ibwami, bararyohewe cane babonye William na Catherine, Harry na Meghan, baseruka bari kumwe
