Inkuru ya Victoria Gill Umunyamakuru w'ubuhinga mu bumenyi, BBC News Abashakashatsi bakurikiranye bakaniga izo nkoto zo mu mashamba y’inzitane yo muri Uganda basanze ivyo bikoko bivuza ingoma ku mizi y’ibiti mu kurungikira ibindi ubutumwa
 Abo bahinga mu bumenyi bavuga yuko umwihariko w’umudiho izo nkoto zivuza utuma zirungika ubutumwa ahantu kure, zigatangaza aho ziri n’izo ari zo, hamwe n’ico ziriko zirakora
 Ivyo vyatahuwe vyasohowe mu kinyamakuru The Journal Animal Behaviour
 Dr Catherine Hobaiter wo kuri kaminuza ya St Andrews muri Scotland yasiguye yuko inkoto zo mw’ishamba zikoresha imizi y’ibiti nk’igice kinini co kuvugirizako ingoma zikoresheje intoke zazo n’ibirenge
 Yabariye ikiganiro Inside Science ca BBC Radio 4 ati : “Iyo ukubise imizi y’igiti n’inguvu nyinshi, irasamirana igasohora ijwi riri hasi, risa n’iriva mu mubindi, rigashika kure mw’ishamba”
 Abandanya agira ati:  “Kenshi twarashobora kumenya [inkoto] iriko iravuza ingoma iyo twayumva; vyari ibintu bihimbaye kuba twarashobora kubona inkoto zitandukanye twarondera
 Rero niba twarashobora kuzimenya, nta gukekeranya ko nazo zamenyana
” Buri nkoto y’ingabo, nk’uko abo bahinga mu bumenyi babibonye, ikoresha umurisho wihariye mu kuvuza ingoma
 Zivanga uwo murisho n’amajwi arangurukira kure azwi mu congereza nka pant-hoots
 Izindi nkoto zica zivuza ingoma mu bihe bitandukanye mu guhamagara kwazo
 Uwayoboye ubu bushakashatsi, umunyeshure wo ku rwego rwa PhD, Vesta Eleuteri, wo kuri kaminuza ya Vienna muri Autriche (Austria), aravuga ukuntu zimwe muri izo nkoto zivuza umudiho wisubiriza cane, wogereranywa n’ingoma zivuzwa muri rock na blues, mu gihe izindi usanga zifise umudiho uhindagurika, nka jazz
 Agira ati: “Naratangaye mbonye nshobora kumenya inkoto yariko iravuza ingoma iyo ari yo nyuma y’indwi nkeyi gusa ndi mw’ishamba”
 Arabandanya ati: “Ariko imidiho y’ingoma zazo irihariye cane ku buryo vyoroshe kuzitandukanya
” Madamu Eleuteri avuga kuri imwe mu nkoto zikiri ntoyi, abashakashatsi bataziriye Tristan, agira ati: “Ni John Bonham (umuhisi yahoze avuza ingoma mu mugwi Led Zeppelin) wo mw’ishamba”
 Ati: "Ivuza umurisho n’inguvu nyinshi cane yungikanya kandi ugashobora kumenya uwo murisho uri kure cane, ukaba rero ushobora no kumenya yuko ari Tristan iriko iravuza ingoma
” Dr Hobaiter agira ati: “Iyo uriko uraratira ubuhinga bwawe ku bagukikuje – iyo uriko iriyereka – urashobora kudashima yuko inkoto y’ingabo ikurusha igikenye iri aho hafi yomenya uwo uri we
 Ntiwoshima gushira ahabona umukenyuro wawe muri ubwo buryo”
 Yongerako yuko gutegera ko inkoto zivuza ingomba muri ubu buryo bishobora kuzotorera umuti ikibazo c’amayobera kimaze igihe kirekire kijanye n’itumanako: inkoto zo mw’ishamba iyo zihuye ziraramukanya, ariko zisa n’izitabwirana “ni agasaga” iyo zivanye ziri mw'ishamba
 Dr Hobaiter arasigura ati: “Inkoto zirashobora kuba zidakenera gusezerana, kuko zirashoboye neza cane kuguma zivugana ziri kure na kure
” “Ubu buryo bwo gutumanako bwa kure buha inkoto ubushobozi bwo kumenya amakuru yazo
 Ivyo birashobora kudufasha gutegera kimwe mu bintu twahora twibaza yuko ari co gishingiyeko ubudasa hagati y’inkoto n’abantu, kandi bikadufasha gutahura igituma ubwo budasa bwoba bwarashitse
”
Umwamikazi Elizabeth II, yari arambiye ku ngoma kurusha abandi mu mateka y'Ubwongereza, yashengeye ari i Balmoral ku myaka 96, nyuma yo kumara ku ngoma imyaka 70
 Umuryango wiwe wahuriye ku kirimba kiri muri Ecosse nyuma yaho amagara yiwe atereye impungenge nyinshi mu gitondo co kuri uno wa kane
 Umwamikazi yimye mu 1952, ku ngoma yiwe hakaba harahindutse vyinshi cane mu buzima bw’igihugu
 Mu gihe atabarutse, umuhungu wiwe mukuru Charles, uwahoze ari Umuganwa wa Wales, azorongora umuhango wo kumwunamira nk’Umwami mushasha akaba n’umukuru w’amaleta 14 y’urunani Commonwealth
 Mu rwandiko, ikirimba ca Buckingham cagize giti: "Umwamikazi yapfuye mu mahoro ari Balmoral ku muhingamo w’uno munsi
 "Umwami n’Umwamikazi wiwe baraguma i Balmoral kuri uno mugoroba bakazosubira i London ejo mu gitondo
" Abana bose b’Umwamikazi bari bagiye i Balmoral, hafi ya Aberdeen, nyuma y’aho abaganga bashiriye Umwamikazi mu bugenduzi bukomeye bw’abaganga
 Umwuzukuru wiwe, Umuganwa William, nawe ni ho ari, hamwe na mwene wabo, Umuganwa Harry
 Ingoma y’Umwamikazi Elizabeth II yabonye ibihe nka vyose vy’intambara, guhinduka kw’ubwami bw’ubwami (Empire) hakaza Commonwealth, kurangira kw’intambara iteruye izwi nka Guerre Froide/Cold War hamwe n’ukwinjira kw’Ubwongereza – no kuva kwabwo – mw’Ishirahamwe rya Buraya
 Ingoma yiwe yabayemwo abashikiranganji ba mbere 15 guhera kuri Winston Churchill, yavutse mu 1874, hamwe na Liz Truss, yavutse imyaka 101 nyuma mu 1975, akaba yaragenywe n’Umwamikazi mu ntango z’ino ndwi
 Yaraha imibonano umushikiranganji wa mbere buri ndwi igihe cose yamaze ku ngoma
 Ku kirimba ca Buckingham Palace i London, isinzi ry’abantu bari barindiriye kumenya amakuru y’Umwamikazi baciye biha amosozi bamaze kumenya inkuru y’urupfu rwiwe
 Umwamikazi yavutse yitwa Elizabeth Alexandra Mary Windsor, avukira i Mayfair, London, itariki 21 Ndamukiza (4) 1926

Perezida Volodymyr Ukraine wa Ukraine avuga ko afise “agakuru keza” ko bigaruriye uturere tutari duke twari mu minwe y’ingabo z‘Uburusiya
 Hari ibihuha vyari bimaze imisi bivuga ko bishoboka ko hari intambwe yatewe mu buseruko bwa Kharkiv, ariko abategetsi ba Ukraine bakaba ataco bari bwashikirize
 Perezida Zelensky ntiyashatse kudoma urutoke ku turere twigaruriwe, akavuga ati “ubu si igihe co kuvuga amazina” yatwo
 Abategetsi ba Amerika bavuga ko Ukraine iriko iratera intambwe bukebuke ariko ikomeye mu rugamba rwo kurwanya ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe yashikirije abanya-Ukraine abicishije kuri videwo nijoro,  Zelensky yavuze ko hari “amakuru meza” ku vyerekeye ibihuha bivuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zateye intambwe
 Ashimagiza ingabo n’ubutwari bwazo ku rugamba, avuga ati: "Ndibaza ko buri munyagihugu yishimira ingabo zacu”
 Ariko, yongerako ati: "Ubu si igihe co kuvuga amazina y’utu turere twasubiye kuduza ibendera rya Ukraine”
 Ukraine yarakomeje ibikorwa vyayo vy’umutekano mu ndwi nkeya ziheze, ariko igatanga amakuru make ku vyerekeye ibikorwa vyo kwivuna vyari birindiriwe mu buseruko no mu bumanuko
 Ingabo za Ukraine zaratanguje urugamba mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Kharkiv, amaja mu ntara ya Donetsk iri mu buseruko, igenzurwa bikomeye n’igisirikare c’Uburusiya kuva intambara itanguye, haraciye amezi atandatu
 Hari amakuru avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zoba ziri hafi y’igisagara ca Izyum, igisagara ngirakamaro mu gushikana ibikoresho ku ngabo z’Uburusiya
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu birori muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Colin Kahl – icegera c’umunyamabanga ajejwe imigambi yo kwivuna abansi – yavuze ko ingabo za Ukraine ziriko ziravyitwaramwo neza gusumba iz’Uburusiya mu turere tumwe tumwe
 Yasubiwemwo n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters  avuga ati: "Haracari kare
 Nibaza ko abanya-Ukraine bariko batera intambwe bukebuke ariko ikomeye
 Tuzoraba ingene bizogenda
 "Ariko ndibaza neza ko ibintu biriko bigenda neza ku ruhande rwa Ukraine muri kino gihe mu bumanuko gusumba uko bimeze ku ruhande rw’Uburusiya”
 Hagati aho, ibintu biracameze nabi
 Igihe vyariko bitanga amakuru y’ingene ibintu vyifashe mw’ijoro ry’ejo ku wa gatatu, ibiro bikuru vya gisirikare vya Ukraine vyavuze ko igisirikare cabo; “Casubije inyuma ibitero vyose vy’Uburusiya” mu ntara za Kharkiv na Donetsk – ariko ko impande zompi zibandanya ziterana vya muzinga n’ibitero vy’indege, ibibanza bitari bike bikaba bihononekarira
 Ejo ku wa gatatu, Perezida Zelensky yavuze kandi ko amafaranga reta ya Ukraine izokoresha mu mwaka uza azoba ari ay’igihugu kiri mu ntambara – aho imiriyaridi 27 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika azoshirwa mu gisata co kwivuna abansi
 Ariko yemeye ko ivya nkenerwa mu mibereho y’abanyagihugu, nk’agafashanyo ko mu za bukuru bizobandanya bitangwa
 Hagati aho, agabisha ati: "Ni nkenerwa kugabanya mu buryo bwose bushoboka ibintu bidakenewe cane, ibintu vyose bidafasha mu kwivuna umwansi, bidafasha mw’iterambere ry’ubutunzi bw’igihugu cacu, mu mubereho n’akaranga vy’abanyagihugu bacu
" Abihweza ibintu n’ibindi muri Amerika no mw’ishirahamwe ONU berekanye amakenga yabo kuri kazoza k’abasivire muri Ukraine mu gihe intambara ibandanya
 Umutegetsi mukuru wo mu gisata kijejwe agateka ka muntu mw’ishirahamwe ONU avuga ko iri shirahamwe rifise impungenge ku bantu bata izabo muri Ukraine – cane cane kazoza k’abana
 Ilze Brands Kehris, icegera c’umunyamabanga mukuru w’ishami rijejwe agateka ka muntu, avuga ati: "Hari amakuru yo kwizera avuga abana batwarwa ku nguvu batari kumwe n’abavyeyi babo mu karere kigaruriwe n’Abarusiya, canke mu Burusiya bwo nyene”
 Ishirahamwe ryiwe rifise amakenga ko Uburusiya bwashinze “uburyo bworoshe” bwo guha abo bana ubwenegihugu bw’Uburusiya, mbere bukabashira mu minwe y’imiryango y’Abarusiya kugira babe ari bo babarera, nk’uko abivuga
 Abona ko iyi ngendo ishobora guhonyanga amasezerano ya Geneva
 Eka na Amerika ifise amakenga nk’aya nyene, aho ejo ku wa gatatu yavuze ko hari abanya-Ukraine, ariko bakuze, batwarwa ku nguvu
 Ibiro vy’ubunyamabanga bujejwe imigenderanire bwagiriza Kremlin ko ifise urutonde rw’abanya-Ukraine bategerezwa gutwarwa ku nguvu mu turere tw’igihugu turi mu minwe y’Uburusiya

