I﻿nyuma y'imyaka 17 Alain Guillaume Bunyoni ari umuntu akomeye mu butegetsi bw'Uburundi, inama nshingamateka yemeje uwumusubirira mu kibanza c'umushikiranganji wa mbere
 K﻿ugira ivyo bibe vyagenze uko ni uko umukuru w'igihugu Evariste Ndayishimiye  atari acishimiye ko babandanya gukorana
 Icatumye Bunyoni akurwa mu mabanga ntikizwi ku mugaragaro
 Ntacavuzwe mu nama nshingamateka igihe yariko iremeza uwumusubirira, nta n'itangazo umukuru w'igihugu yasohoye kugira avuge imvo z'uko atari acifuza ko bandanya gukorana
 K﻿andi ntibwari kuba bubaye ubwa mbere havugwa ico umutetegetsi ahowe mu kubogozwa mu mabanga
 Gusa biragoye kutabiha isano no kuba vyashitse umukuru w’igihugu Evariste Ndayishimiye yaheruka kuvuga ko hari abantu “bigira ibihangange”, mbere ko hari abamukangisha kumukubita coup d’etat
 Uko biri kwose, ikurwa rya Alain Guillaume Bunyoni rishobora kuba ryari rirangije imyaka yiwe myinshi mu bibanza bikomeye vy’ubutegetsi bwa CNDD-FDD kuva uwo mugambwe utanguye kuramutswa igihugu mu 2005
 Iyo ntwazangabo y’ipete rya mbere rihanitse mu gipolisi c’Uburundi yagiye arakuranya ibibanza bitandukanye mu butegetsi bw’inzego z’igihugu
 Mu myaka 15 umuhisi prezida Pierre Nkurunziza yamaze ku butegetsi (2005-2020), Alain Guillaume Buyoni yabaye: Imbere y’uko aba n’umushikiranganji wa mbere, Bunyoni yari ageze aho biboneka aho aciye ko atari umushikiranganji nk’abandi
 Yagendera mu rukurikirane rw’imiduga myinshi kurusha abandi bashikiranganji bose
 Yinjiye mw’iduka ibarabara rica imbere yaryo ryarugarwa hepfo no haruguru, abari imbere mw’iduka bakagumayo, abari hanze bakarindira bose gushika ahejeje icari kimujanye akagenda
 Alain-Guillaume Bunyoni bivugwa ko ari mu bantu batunze cane
 Ibimenyetso vy’ubwo butunzi bimwe bimwe ntiyabinyegeza nko mu kugaragaza amafoto agabira imodoka z’agaciro umugore n’abana biwe iyo bagize amasabukuru, canke mu kwifotoza be n’umugore mu nzu zabo bicaye mu ntebe canke bambaye ivyambarwa bigaragara ko ari ivy’agaciro
 Alain-Guillaume w’imyaka 50, yavukiye muri komine Kanyosha mu ntara ya Bujumbura mu 1972, ariko mu nyuma umuryango wiwe wahavuye wimukira mu ntara ya Rutana, aho afise urugo runini
 Yagiye ava kuri kaminuza y’Uburundi aja mu muhari warwana wa CNDD-FDD inyuma y’igandagurwa ry’umukuru w’igihugu Melchior Ndadaye mu 1993
 U﻿wo muhari wahavuye uhinduka umugambwe utwara igihugu kuva mu 2005, kuva ico gihe Bunyoni akaba yari amaze iyo myaka yose (17) mu bibanza bikomeye vy'ubwo butegetsi
 K﻿o ikibanza ciwe mu butegetsi bw'igihugu coba kigarukiye ngaho, haracari kare kubimenya

Ku ncuro ya mbere  kuva Uburundi  buvuye mu bukoroni bw’Ububirigi haraheze imyaka 60,  intumwa z’Ububirigi zaje muri ico gihugu mu gikorwa co gutohoza kuri ako kahise karanzwe n’amabi menshi
 Ni gikorwa kizoba kandi mu Rwanda no muri Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo navyo vyatwawe gikoroni n'Ububirigi
 Uwo mugwi udasanzwe w'inama nshingamateka y'Ububirigi ku wa kabiri wagendeye  ubwa mbere inama nshingamateka y'Uburundi
 Umukuru wawo Wouter De Vriendt yamenyesheje ko washinzwe mu 2020 ukaba ujejwe: Wakiriwe n'umukuru w'inama nshingamateke y'Uburundi, Gelase Ndabirabe,  ari kumwe n'ibiro vy'inama arongoye n'abakuru b'imigwi itandukanye iri muri urwo rwego
 Hari kandi n'abatumire bamwe bamwe nk'umukuru w'umugwi ujejwe kumenya ukuri ku mabi yashikiye Uburundi kuva ku gihe c'ubokoroni
 Umukuru w'inama nshingamateka y'Uburundi, Gelase Ndabirabe, yabwiye uwo mugwi ko 'twebwe abakoronijwe dufise vyinshi vyo kubabwira"
 Ndabirabe yasomeye izo ntumwa amabi y’agahomerabumwa abakoroni b’ababirigi bakoreye Uburundi n’ibindi bihugu vyose  baciyemwo
 Harimwo, kwica, gusahura itunga ry'igihugu, kubiba amacakubiri, ariko na cane cane gufata uwukolonijwe nk’uwufise agaciro kari munsi y’ak'igikoko
 Ati: "Koko muturaba amaso mu yandi, mubona tutari ibiremwa-bantu? "Mubona ko tudafise ubwenge, ko vyari bikwiye ko mudukorera amabi nk'ayo mwadukoreye?" Umukuru w’inama nshingamateka yabumvishije ijwi ry’umwami w’ababirigi Leopold Wa Kabiri aho yariko aratuma abamenyeshamana gukoresha ijambo ry'Imana mu gukorera amabi abanye-Congo no kubumvisha ko bategerezwa kuyemera no kuyihanganira kugira "bazokwinjire mu bwami bw'Imana"
 "Kandi niko mwabikoze n'ahandi" nk'uko yababwiye
 Umwami w'Ababirigi Leopold II yamaze imyaka irenga 20 -kuva mu 1885 gushika mu 1908- ikiri ubu Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo yakigize icibare (itongo) ciwe bwite imbere y'uko agishikiriza reta y'Ububirigi
 Uburundi n'Urwanda (Rwanda-Urundi) vyo vyahawe Ububirigi inyuma y'intambara ya kabiri y'isi yose (1914-1918) Ubudagi buhejeje gustindwa
