 Nk’uko icegeranyo c’igendereza cashizwe ahabona kigashikira ikinyamakuru New York Times kibivuga, Uburusiya bwaguze i Pyongyang amamiriyoni y’ibibombe na vya muzinga
 Umutegetsi wa Amerika avuga ko bishobora kuba ngombwa ko Uburusiya bugura ibindi birwanisho vya Korea ya Ruguru mu gihe intambara ibandanya
 Mu ndwi iheze, bivugwa ko Moscou yakiriye igice ca mbere c'indege  zitagira abadereva (drones) zivuye muri Irani
 Irani na Korea ya Ruguru, vyompi vyafatiwe ibihano bikomeye n’Uburengero, biriko birondera gutsimbataza ubucuti n’Uburusiya kuva Perezida Vladimir Putin atanguje igitero kuri Ukraine mu kwa kabiri
 Ubutegetsi bwa Kim Jong-un bwagiriza Amerika ko ari yo yateje iyi ntambara, bwagiriza kandi Uburengero ko bubandanya “ingendo yo kwiyagurira uturere” ari yo yatumye Uburusiya bukoresha inguvu
 Mu kwezi guheze, Korea ya Ruguru yaremeje ukwikukira kw’intara zibiri zegamiye ku Burusiya mu buseruko bwa Ukraine – Repubulika za Donetsk na Luhansk – mbere ica yiyemeza gutsimbataza “ubucuti” na Moscou
 Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya avuga ko ibi bihugu bibiri bishobora kwagura “ubucuti bwavyo vyompi”, nk’uko bivugwa n’ibinyamakuru vya Pyongyang vyegamiye reta
 Iki cegeranyo ntigisobanura neza ibirwanisho nyezina bizotangwa
 Ariko umutegetsi wa Amerika yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru Associated Press ko kubona Uburusiya bwikoze kuri Korea ya Ruguru kugira ibufashe vyerekana ko “igisirikare c’Uburusiya kibandanya kigira ingorane z’ubukene bw’ibikoresho muri Ukraine, kubera igenzurwa ry’ibidandazwa bushora hanze hamwe n’ibihano”
 Ikigo c’ubushakashatsi co muri Finland, Centre for Research on Energy and Clean Air,  kivuga ko ibihano ku butunzi ata kintu kinini vyononye ku mwimbu Uburusiya bukura mu bitanganguvu bushora hanze
 Kigereranya ko Uburusiya bwinjije ama-euro imiriyaridi 158 mu gitoro n’ibindi bitanganguvu (fossil fuels/combustibles fossils) bigenda vyiyongera, mu mezi atandatu y’iyi ntambara, mu gihe ivyinjira mu bihugu vy’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya birenga ica kabiri c’ayo mafaranga
 Hagati aho, Amerika n’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya, vyemeza ko ubushobozi bwa Moscou bwo kwongereza inguvu z’igisirikare cayo bwahungabanijwe
 Mu ndwi iheze, abategetsi bo mu ntwaro ya Joe Biden babwiye ibinyamakuru vya Amerika ko indege za mbere za drones zatanzwe na Irani zageze mu Burusiya
 Abategetsi bajejwe igendereza rya Amerika bemeza ko abadereva b’Uburusiya bagiye muri Irani kugira bahabwe inyigisho z’ingene bakoresha ibirwanisho vyo mu bwoko bwa Mohajer-6 na Shahed
 Ariko bari baherutse kubwira abanyamakuru ko nyinshi muri izo drones zagize ibibazo vya mekanike na tekniki kuva zitanzwe
 Irani irahakana ko ata birwanisho yahaye uruhande na rumwe muri iyo ntambara, ariko mu kw’indwi umuhanuzi mukuru wa Amerika mu vyo umutekano Jake Sullivan yavuze ko Tehran yariko irategura kurungikira Moscou drones ziharurwa mu majana zari gukoreshwa mu ntambara yayo muri Ukraine, zimwe muri zo zifise ubushobozi bwo gukora ibitero
 Kuri uno wa kabiri, abategetsi bo mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Ubwongereza bavuze ko Uburusiya bufise ingorane zo kurungika drones z’intambara bitewe n’uko “buriko buratakaza” bikomeye
 Bavuga bati: "Bisa n’uko Uburusiya bufise ingorane zo kubungabunga indege zitagira abadereza bufise mu bubiko, bikunyurwa n’ubukene bwazo butewe n’ibihano bwafatiwe n’amakungu”
 Abategetsi bongerako bati: "Kuba indege zitagira abadereva zitaboneka bikwiye bishobora kubangamira intwazangabo mu nteguro zabo kandi bikananiza ibikorwa vy’Uburusiya”

Igipolisi ca Canada kivuga ko umwe mu bantu babiri bikekwa ko ari bo bakoze igitero c’imbugita bakica bamwe mu bantu bari mu misa ku wa Mungu yatowe yapfuye
 Ikiziga ca Damien Sanderson w’imyaka 31 catowe mu karere ka James Smith Cree Nation, ari nako abatari bake mu bishwe bari batuyemwo, nk’uko igipolisi kibimenyesha
 Aba bantu babiri bikekwa baravukana, igipolisi kikavuga ko Myles Sanderson acinyegeje, akaba azwi ko ari mu gisagara ca Regina
 Ku wa Mungu, abantu cumi barishwe bacumiswe imbugita muri kimwe mu bitero vy’ubugizi bwa nabi bikomeye muri ino myaka ya vuba muri Canada
 Ibi bitero – vyakomerekeyemwo kandi abandi bantu 18 – vyabereye mu karere kari mu mitumba ya kure mu ntara ya Saskatchewan
 Muri Regina, umugwa mukuru w’intara, ari naho aba bikekwa gukora iki gitero babonetse ubwa nyuma, imiryango igandariye abayo mu gihe abanyagihugu baho barangwa n’umujinya
 Hagati aho, mu gisagara hagati  ku mugoroba w’ejo ku wa mbere, nta kintu na kimwe cerekana ko hari abariko baronderwa
 Igisagara cari gitekanye mu gihe imiryango yari yateranye yigina umusi mukuru w’abakozi, umusi urangiza igihe c’ici
 Ku ncuro zitari nke, iri tuze ryagiye rihungabanywa n’amajwi y’igabisha ku materefone ngendanwa, yagabisha ko hari abantu babiri bikekwa bariko bararonderwa, mu nyuma umwe gusa akaba ari we yari akironderwa
 Abapolisi bo mu ntara zitatu - Saskatchewan, Manitoba na Alberta – nibo bari muri uru ruhigi
 Ubwicanyi bw’agahomerabunwa bubandanya buhungabanya iyi ntara yari isanzwe itekanye, aho igipolisi kiriko kirakora amatohoza ku bugizi bwa nabi bwabaye mu turere 13 dutandukanye
 Damien na Myles bose bagiriwe n’icaha c’ubwicanyi, n’aho batarafatwa
 Mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru, icegera ca komiseri w’igipolisi Rhonda Blackmore yavuze ko "uyu mugabo yapfuye " yatowe ahitwa James Smith Cree Nation ejo ku wa mbere isaha zitanu n’igice zo mu gitondo, (isaha imwe n’igice z’ijoro mu masaha yo mu Burundi no mu Rwanda)
 Vyahavuye vyemezwa ko “ico kiziga ari ica Damien Sanderson"
 Yabwiye abanyamakuru ko iki kiziga catowe mw’ishamba ryinshi hafi y’inzu yariko irakorwako amatohoza”, n’abategetsi
 Umupfasoni Blackmore avuga ko ikiziga ca Damien basanze gifise ibikomere kandi ko “biboneka ko atari we yikomerekeje”
 Igipolisi kivuga ko Myles, mwenewabo wa Damien, akiriko araronderwa, kigasaba abanyagihugu kuguma bameze magabo
 Uyu mugabo w’imyaka 30 yikekwa ko ari we yakoze iki gitero ashobora kuba na we nyene yarakomeretse, igipolisi kikagabisha ko ashobora kurondera ingene yivuza
 Ariko igipolisi ntikivuga nimba yoba ari we yishe mwenewabo
 Myles, yigeze kuba azwi mu gipolisi, avugwa ko “azwi cane mu bugizi bwa nabi” kuva mu myaka itari mike aho yagirizwa ubukozi bw’ikibi yakora ku bantu n’ibintu
 Abenshi mu bishwe bava mu karere ko mu mitumba ya kure James Smith Cree Nation gasanzwe gatuwemwo n’abantu bababa 2000 – abanyagihugu b’abasangwabutaka ba Canada bakaba batekewe n’ubwoba
 Hatangajwe ibihe bidasanzwe mu ntara ya Saskatchewan
 Ibinyamakuru vya Canada vyamenye bamwe mu bishwe, n’aho ata nsiguro ziratangwa n’ubutegetsi
 Abanyagihugu ba Saskatchewan bangana n’imiriyoni 1
2 bakwiragiye ku butaka bwa kirometero kwadarato 647
497
 Imiryango ifitaniye ubucuti bwa hafi ikwiragiye irya n’ino mu turere tw’indimo dutandukanijwe n’amarabaraba
 Twinshi muri utu turere tubona ko turi iyo catawe

