 Tom Tugendhat, umushingamateka akaba n’umukuru w’umugwi w’inama nshingamatela y’Ubwongereza ujejwe ivy’imigenderanire n’amakungu, yavuze yuko ivyo iki cegeranyo cabonye birimwo "ibirego bikomeye cane" aniyamiriza ibivugwa na Beijing vy’uko ivyo vyagiriji birondera urwanko ku Bushinwa
