Abashigikiye umugambi wa Trump “Make America Great Again” (Maga) barageramiye demokrasi, vyaraye bivuzwe n’umukuru wa Amerika Joe Biden
 “Abashigikiye Maga bashaka gusubiza iki gihugu inyuma,” niko Biden yavuze mw’ijambo yashikirije mu gihe tevelivison iba iriko irarabwa n’abantu benshi cane, akaba yari muri Pennsylvania
 Umukuru w’aba-Republicain (umugambwe wa Trump)  Kevin McCarthy, nawe yarashikirije ijambo ryiwe, avuga ko Biden “yakomerekeje cane umushaha wa Amerika”
 Ayo majambo abiri abangabanganwa yavuzwe mu gihe hasigaye amezi abiri ngo habe amatora yo hagati mu kiringo (mid-term canke mi-mandat) , amatora avamwo kubona ingene ubwiganze bumeze mu butegetsi bwa Washington
 Prezida wa Amerika ijambo ryiwe yarishikirije ku wa kane mw’ijoro ari ahitwa Independence Hall muri Philadelphia, ahashiriwe umukono kw’itangazo ry’ukwikukira kwa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika
 Yagarutse ku civuga ciwe co mu matora yo mu 2020 co kugarukana ”umushasha wa Amerika”
 Yavuze ko  atiyamiriza Abanyamerika bose bashika miriyoni 74 batoye Trump haraheze imyaka ibiri
 Yavuze ati:  “Umu-Republicain wese si umu-Maga, mbere n’ubwiganze bw’aba-Republicain si aba-Maga”
 Yabandanije ati: “Ariko si ivyo kubaza,  ubu umuganbwe w’aba-Republicain wifatiwe kandi   ugoswe na Trump n’aba-Maga, ivyo rero birageramiye igihugu
” Biden yavuze ko abashigikiye Trump bibaza bibaza ko abateye Capitol mu mwaka uheze ari abakunda igihugu aho gufata ko ari abagumutsi
 Yabandanije ati: “Mu  gihe kitari gito, twagumye twibaza ko demokrasi ya Amerika ataho ikija
 Ivyo si vyo
 Dutegerezwa kuyirwanira
 Kuyikingira
 Tukayihagararira
 Umwe umwe wese muri twebwe
” Yishura, Trump yashigikiye icivugo ciwe ca Maga  hanyuma avuga ko umukeba wiwe ari we “ageramiye Amerika”
 Mu gihe cose Biden yariko arashikiriza ijambo, hari umuntu yagumye avuza inzamba, nk’uko bivugwa n’umunayamakuru wa BBC yari ahari
 Prezida Biden yagize ico abivugako kabiri, irya kabiri avuga ati :” Bafise uburenganzira bwo kurakara
 Iyi ni demokrasi
” Biden yashitse ku butegetsi avuga ko aje kwunga igihugu, agize igihe yakajije imvugo yiwe ku bashigikiye Trump
 Ku ndwi iheze, Biden yagereranije ico yise aba-Republicain bakaze no  kuba begeranye na “faschism”
 McCarthy, arongoye aba-Republicain ubu badafise ubwiganze mu nama nshingamateka, yari yavuze imbere, ari mu gisagara c’amavukiro ca Biden ca Scranton muri Pennsylvania
 Uwo mushingamateka wo muri California yavuze ko umukuru w’igihugu “yahisemwo gucanishamwo, gutesha agaciro benewewabo b’abanyamerika”
 “Kubera iki? Ni ukubera batemera imigambi yiwe
 Ubwo si uburongozi
” Yasavye Biden “gusaba imbabazi ku kwambika ibara miriyoni z’abanyamrika mu kubita aba-faschist”
 Umukuru w’aba-Republicain yavuze ko ubutegetsi bwa Biden bwatumye abanyamerika bugarizwa n’iduga ry’ibiciro, imbibe zuguruye, amashure yugawe mu gihe ca Covid aguhangabanya ivyigwa vy’abana, ukuva muri Afghanistan kwabaye mu kajagari , hamwe n’ubwicanyi mu gihugu kuruta ikindi gice cose mu myaka 20
 Yabandanije ati: “Mu myaka ibiri iheze, Joe Biden yarabbaje umushasha wa Amerika, abanyagihugu bayo, amategeko yayo, n’ingengagaciro za mbere ntakorwako
 Yarababaje, imigambi yiwe yarakomerekeje cane umushasha wa Amerika, isubiza hasi agatima ka Amerika kandi arahemukira icizere ca Amerika
 Trump nawe yongereje ikineguro kw’ijambo rya  Biden mu butumwa yanditse ku rubuga hwaniro rwiwe
 Yanditse ati: “Niba adashaka gusubiza Amerika kuba igihangange, ivyo navyo mu majambo, mu bikorwa, mu vyiyumviro akaba atabishaka, aho rero nta nkeka ntakwiye kuva ahagarariye  Reta Zunze za Amerika
” Ariko abitaba amatora bavuganye na BBC mu gisagara gitoya ca Newfoundland ku 190km mu buraruko bw’aho Joe Biden yavugiye ijambo, nta mpungenege berekanye zo kuba demokrasi igeramiwe nk’uko yabivuze
 Igiciro c’ibitoto niwo wari umwitwarariko w’abanyamerika aho bari mw’ihayanishwa muri iyo ntara
 Abanyamerika benshi berekanye ubudasa bw’ubutunzi mu gihe ca Trump n’ubu
 Ariko hari umuntu yavuze ko yabaye umu-Republicain ubuzima bwiwe bwose yavuze ko atazokwigera atora Trump canke abo bose azoba ashigikiye
 Izina rya Trump nta na hamwe rizoba ryanditse ku mpapuro zo gutora, ariko kuba ahari ntibizohara
 Mu mpera z’iyi ndwi niwe azoba arongoye ikoraniro rya poritike mu karere ka  Scranton
 Benshi mu ba-Republicain bitoza  muri iyi ntara baronse amajwi yo kwitoza kubera bashigikiwe n’uwo yahora ari umukuru w’igihugu

Abashingwamanza ba Aung San Suu Kyi bavuga ko sentare ya gisirikare ya Myanmar yamuciriye iyindi myaka itatu y'igipfungo yagirizwa ubusuma mu matora
 Suu Kyi - yahoze arongoye ico gihugu - ubu amaze gucirirwa gupfungwa imyaka 20 ku vyaha 11, mu gihe hagisigaye ibindi vyaha yagirizwa vyinshi
 Arahakana ivyo vyose yagirizwa, kandi izo manza acibwa zagumye ziyamirizwa  n'amashirahamwe aharanira agateka ka zina muntu, avuga ko zinyegeje inyuma ya politike
 Mu gihe yohamwa n'ivyaha  vyose, ashobora gucirirwa gupfungwa imyaka yoba ishika 200
 Ico gihano gishasha kirimwo no gukora ibikorwa biruhisha, nk'uko bivugwa n'abamuburanira
 Uwo mugore w'imyaka 77 yatsindiye agashimwe kitiriwe Nobel amaze umwanya munini w'ubuzima bwiwe apfunzwe icamaso ku muhana iwe , ku mugwa mukuru Nay Pyi Taw
 Abantu hamwe n'abamenyeshamakuru ntibarekuriwe gukurikirana urwo rubanza rwabera mu mwiherero kandi igisirikare cari cabujije abamuburanira kuvugana n'abamenyeshamakuru
 Sentare yamuhamije icaha c'ubusuma mu matora rusangi yo mu kwezi wa cumi na rimwe mu 2020, aho umugambwe wiwe, National League for Democracy (NLD), watsinze n'amajwi menshi
 Igisirikare catembagaje ubutegetsi mu mwaka uheze, citwaje ko habaye ubusuma bw'amajwi mu matora, ariko abahagarikizi b'amatora bavuga ko ivyayavuyemo " vyari vyisunze ivyipfuzo vy'abanyagihugu"
 Amashirahamwe aharanira agateka ka zina muntu na demokrasi yariyamirije ikurikiranwa rya Suu Kyi hamwe n'abandi avuga ko ivyo bagirizwa bitagira umutwe n'amaguru
 ONU/UN ivuga ko ari imbere y'"urubanza ruteye isoni"
 Intwaro ya gisirikare ivuga ko urubanza rwa Suu Kyi rukurikije amategeko
 Umuvugizi w'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu riharanira agateka ka zina muntu, Amnesty International yabwiye BBC ko igisirikare gikoresha uburyo bwemewe n'amategeko nk'"ikindi gikoresho mu bindi vyinshi co gushaka gucinyiza abatavuga rumwe na bo"
 Uwo muvugizi yagize ati:"Imanza z'urutavanako za Aung San Suu Kyi ni kamwe mu turorero k'ingene igisirikare cagize sentare ikirwanisho mu kwinyegeza inyuma ya politike canke ibindi bitagira umutwe n'amaguru mu kwagiriza abatavuga rumwe na co n'abagira imyiyerekano
" Ifatwa ku nguvu ry'ubutegetsi n'abasirikare mu kwezi kwa kabiri ryatumye hakwiragira imyiyerekano, bituma abasirikare bari ku butegetsi i Myanmar bahiga buhongo abashigikiye demokrasi bari mu myiyerekano, abaharanira agateka ka zina muntu hamwe n'abamenyeshamakuru
 Suu Kyi - hamwe n'abandi bayoboke b'umugambwe wiwe - bari mu bandi bantu barenga 15
000 b'ahagaritswe n'igisirikare kuva bafashe ubutegetsi - abashika 12
000 baracari mw'ibohero, nk'uko bivugwa n'ishirahamwe rifasha abanye politike bari mw'ibohero (Assistance Association for Political Prisoners)
 Ku musi wa gatanu, uwahoze aserukira Ubwongereza muri Myanmar n'umugabo wiwe baciriwe gupfungwa umwaka wose umwe wese yagirizwa kurenga ku mategeko agenga abimukira
 Vicky Bowman, yaserukiye Ubwongereza muri Myanmar kuva mu 2002 gushika 2006, hamwe n'umunyabugenegene Htein Lin bahagaritswe  mu ndwi iheze ku muhana wabo i Yangon

Umushikiranganji wa Afrika y’Epfo ajejwe amagara y’abantu yagabishije abanyagihugu ko atari bo bajejwe kwubahiriza amategeko agenga abanyamahanga
 Joe Phaahla yabivuze igihe yagendera ibitaro vyo ku murwa mukuru, Pretoria, aho abantu bo mu mugwi wiyita Operation Dudula bagize  imyiyerekano bagerageza kubuza abanyamahanga kwivuza
 Uwo mugwi Operation Dudula wagirizwa kwanka abanyamahanga, ariko abanywanyi bawo bavuga ko abanyamahanga batuma  amavuriro n’ibitaro vy’igihugu cabo birengerwa
 Phaahla yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ko abantu bava mu bihugu bibanyi – eka mbere no mu vya kure nk’Ubuhindi – baza kwivuza muri Afrika y’Epfo
 Yavuze ko ivyo bibandanije gutyo, Afrika y’Epfo izoshika aho irengerwa
 Ariko yashimangiye ko ibwirizwa nshingiro ritomoye ku burenganzira bwo kwivuza ku muntu wese aba muri Afrika y’Epfo
 Abagiye mu myiyerekano babandanije gusaba ko abantu babanza kwerekana ubwenegihugu bwabo imbere y’uko binjira ibitaro n’ubwo hari ingingo ya sentare ibihagarika
 Bivugwa ko abantu b’urukoba (uruhu) rwirabura aribo batotwa hanyuma bagahatirwa kwerekana ko bazi kuvuga rumwe mu ndimi zisanzwe zivugwa aho muri Afrika y’Epfo
 Ku wa kane hadutse intureka hagati y‘abanywanyi ba Operation Dudula n’abadashigikiye iyo myiyerekano hanze y’ivyo bitaro
 Igiporisi carashe amasasu ya caoutchouc kugira gishwiragize  iyo migwi ibiri
 Reta ya Afrika y’Epfo ntisanzwe iharura abanyamahanga baja kwivuza mu mavuriro y’igihugu
 Ariko hari impungenge ku ngaruka abanyamahanga b’abimukira batagira ibibaranga bashobora kugira ku nzego z’ubuvuzi muri ico gihugu
 Muri Afrika y'Epfo si ubwa mbere havuzwe ikibazo co kwanka abanyamahanga
 Mu kwezi kwa gatatu uyu mwaka, abanywanyi ba Alexandra Dudula Movement bagize imyirekano bavuga ko abanyamahanga bigaruriye amazu ya reta
 Muri iyo myiyerekano bari bafise ivyapa bimwe bivuga ngo   "tahe iwanyu" 

