Umuntu wa nyuma yari asigaye mu mugwi umwe w'abantu b'abasangwabutaka muri Brezil yapfuye  nk'uko bimenyeshwa n'abategetsi
 Uwo mugabo ataramenyekana izina, yari amaze imyaka 26 yibana
 Yari azwi kw'izina ry'"Umuntu wa mbere yibana wenyene kw'isi" kubera yimvye ibinogo birebire, bimwe bimwe yakoresha mu gutega ibikoko, mu gihe ibindi wasanga avyinyegezamwo
 Ikiziga ciwe catowe itariki 23 z'ukwezi kw'umunani mu vyatsi imbere y'akaruri kiwe yari yubakishije ivyatsi
 Nta kintu na kimwe cerekana ko hoba hariho abahagwaniye
 Uwo muntu yari uwa nyuma mu mugwi w'abasangwabutaka, aho abandi bantu batandatu b'uwo mugwi wiwe bari basigaye  bishwe mu 1995
 Abo bantu babaye mu karere k'aba Tanaru mu ntara ya Rondônia, ihana urubibe na Bolivia
 Vyibazwa ko benshi mubo mu bwoko bwiwe bishwe kera nko mu myaka ya 1970 n'aborozi bashaka kwagura aho baragira
 Uwo muntu yari afise imyaka nka 60 yazize urupfu rusanzwe
 Nta kimenyetso na kimwe cerekana ko hari uwamuteye aho yaba kandi nta kintu na kimwe cononekaye aho nyene yaba, nk'uko bivugwa n'abategetsi, ariko n'aho biri uko igipolisi kizopima ikiziga ciwe
 Nk'uko biri mw'ibwirizwa shingiro rya Brezil, abantu b'abasangwabutaka barafise uburenganzira ku matongo yabo, rero abashaka kuyabatwara ni bo baca babica
 "Uwo muntu yibana wenyene" yahora acungerewe kubera umutekano wiwe n'abantu bo mu gisata ca Brezil kijejwe abasangwabutaka kuva mu mwaka wa 1996
 Mu 2018, umuntu umwe yarigeze kumufata isanamu igihe yariko aragwana n'igikoko co mw'ishamba
 Kuri iyo foto, aboneka ariko ararunguruka ku giti, afise ikintu kimeze nk'ishoka
