Uburusiya bwahagaritse rwose kurungika gaz i Buraya  iciye mu muringoti munini, buvuga ko ukeneye gusanurwa
 Kompanyi rutura y’Uburusiya ishinzwe amasoko ntanganguvu, Gazprom, yavuze ko guhagarika kurungika gaz iciye mu muringoti  Nord Stream 1  bizomara iminsi itatu
 Uburusiya bwari busanzwe bumaze kugabanya cane gaz burungika i Buraya iciye muri uwo muringoti
 Ariko burahakana ivyo bwagirizwa ko buriko burakoresha gaz busanzwe bugurisha nk’inzira yo guhana ibihugu vya Buraya kubera ibihano  vyabufatiye kuva aho butereye Ukraine
 Umuringoti Nord Stream 1 ureha na 1
200km ugaca munsi y’ikiyaga ca Baltic kuva ku nkengera z’Uburusiya hafi ya St Petersburg gushika mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw’Ubudagi
 Wuguruwe mu 2011, kandi ushobora kurungika metero kibe (m3 ) miriyoni 17 za gaz ku munsi kuva mu Burusiya gushika mu Budagi
 Uwo muringoti wari wugawe mu kiringo c’iminsi 10 mu kwezi kwa Mukakaro (70)- naho nyene kubera ibikorwa vyo kuwusanura- muri iyi minsi wari wasubiye gukora kuri 20% y’ubushibozi bwawo  ku mvo Uburusiya buvuga ko ari ivyuma bidakora neza
 Umukuru  w’urwego rugenzura uruhererkane [rw’inguvu]  mu Budagi yavuze ko igihugu  kizoshobora kuvyifatamwo neza- hamwe Uburusiya bwoca busubira kurungika iyo gaz mu minsi iza
 Klaus Mueller yabwiye Reuters ati: “Ndazi ko tuzoshobora kuvyitwaramwo
 “Nizeye ko Uburusiya buzosubira kurungika 20% ku wa gatandatu, ariko nta n’umwe yoshobora kuvyemeza
” Abategetsi ba Buraya bafise ubwoba ko Uburusiya bushobora kwongereza igihe co kutarungika gaz mu kugerageza gutuma ibiciro vya gaz biduga, mu gihe bisanzwe vyaraduze cane muri uyu mwaka uheze
 Iryo duga rikabije rishobora gutuma ubuzima buzimba cane mu gihe c’imbeho nyinshi (hiver), ama reta aakaba yoca ategerezwa gusohora za miriyaridi z’amafaranga kugira  zunganire abanyagihugu
 Ku wa kabiri, umushikiranganji w’Ubufaransa ajejwe kwijukira ayandi masoko ntanganguvu, Agnes Pannier-Runacher, yagirije Uburusiya “gukoresha gaz nk’ikigwanisho co mu ntambara”
 Yavuze inyuma y’aho Gazprom ivugiye ko izohagarika kurungikira gaz kompanyi y’Ubufaransa Engie
 Ariko umuvugizi wa prezida w’Uburusiya Vladmir Putin yiyamirije ivyo bagirizwa – ashimangira ko ibihano vy’ibihugu vya Buraya  arivyo vyateye izo ngorane mu gutuma ibikorwa remezo vy’Uburusiya vyononekera
 Yashimitse avuga ko “ingirane z’ubuhinga” zatewe n’ibihano nico kintu conyene zibuza Uburusiya kurungika gaz iciye muri uwo muringoti, ariko ntasobanura izo ngorane izo arizo
 Kimwe mu vyateye impari cane ni turbine yashitse mu Budagi ivuye gusanurwa muri Canada ariko Uburusiya buranka gusubira kuyakira, buvuga ko nayo yafashwe n’ibihano vy’abanyaburaya
 Ubudagi ariko ivyo Ubudagi burabihakana
 Muri uku kwezi, umukuru w’urwego rutwara ishirahamwe rya Buraya, Ursula von der Leyen, yemeye kugira uruhara mu masoko ntanganguvu, avugira mu kiganiro muri Slovenia ko amasoko ahasanzwe atagihuye n’ivyo bakeneye
 Yavuze ati : “ Dukeneye isoko ry’umuyagankuba ritunganijwe ukundi rikora vy’ukuri kandi rituma dusubira kuja hagati na hagati”
 Imbere y’intambara, Ubudagi bwari bwemeje miriyaridi 10 z’ama euro zo kwubka umuringoti Nord Stream 2, ugenda ubangabanganwa  n’uwo vyitiranwa- ariko buca buhagarika ibikorwa inyuma y’aho Uburusiya burungikiye ingabo muri Ukraine mu kwezi kwa Ruhuhuma(2)
 Ku ndwi iheze, BBC yerekanye ko Uburusiya bwariko buraturira gaz igereranywa ku gaciro ka miriyaridi 10 z’ama dorari  mu ruganda ruri hafi y’urubiba na Finlande

Abantu batari munsi ya 80 baranyurujwe baraburwa irengero mu Burundi mu myaka ibiri iheze kuva prezida Evariste Ndayishimiye ashitse ku butegetsi  biri mw'ikete ishirahamwe Focode ryarungikiye umukuru w'Uburundi mu gihe amakungu yibuka abantu banyuruzwa bakaburwa irengero kw'itariki ya 30 Myandagaro (8)
 Muri iryo kete Focode isaba prezida  Evariste Ndayishimiye gushira  mu ngiro amajambo meza avuga yo gukingira abanyagihugu amabi bene ayo
 BBC Gahuzamiryango yarondeye kumenya ico ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu bivuga kuri iryo kete
 Umuvugizi w’umukuru w’igihugu, Alain Diomede Nzeyimana yishuye ati: ”Ishirahamwe ritemewe n'amategeko ivyo ryanditse nibo biraba, ça n'engage personne d'autre [nta wundi n’umwe abibazwa]
 Ishirahamwe Focode, Forum pour la Conscience et le Développement, riri mu yafuswe mu Burundi, ariko rikomeza gukorera hanze
 Mu 2016, ryatanguje umugambi "Ndondeza" wo gukurwanya amabi yo kunyuruza abantu
 Igereranije n’imyaka ibiri y’imbere y’uko prezida Ndayishimiye ashika ku butegetsi, Focode isanga ukunyuruza abantu vyiyongeye ku rugero rwa 38%
 Focode ivuga ko abayuruzwa yobashira  mu migwi mikuru mikuru 5: Focode ivuga ko abo ari abo yashoboye kumenya ikanakorako amatohoza
 Yibaza ko igitigiri c’abanyuruzwa gishobora kuba kirenga ngaho
 Ivuga ko "imiryango myinshi ihitamwo kunuma iyo abayo babuzwe irengero mu gutinya inkurikizi, hari n’imiryango itamenya ko abayo banyurujwe”
 Focode isanga mu bagirizwa ayo mabi hari icahindutse kuva hatanguye ubutegetsi bwa Prezida Ndayishimiye
 Mu gihe imbere yiwe ingabo zijejwe  gucungera umutekano w’mukuru w’igihugu zaza imbere, ubu ngo ntizikivugwa mu banyuruza abantu
 Ariko ahanini izo Focode ivuga muri iryo kete ni izikunzwe gutungwa n’amashirahamwe aharanira agateka ka zina muntu
 Rikurikije amatohoza yaryo, ishirahamwe Focode risanga abavugwa muri mabi yo kunyuruza abantu batonze gutya mu banyurujwe muri iyo myaka ibiri: Focode ivuga ko agishika ku butegetsi, umukuru w’igihugu Evariste Ndayishimiye yavuga nka reta yahahora mu guhakana ko ata mabi yo kunyuruza abantu akorwa
 Muri iryo kete yamwandikiye, Focode ivuga ko hari  icahindutse mu mvugo yiwe
 Iryo shirahamwe rivuga ko umunsi yagirisha inama abarundi baba mu bindi bihugu i Ngozi mu kwezi kw’indwi mu 2022, umukuru w’igihugu yavuze ko vyamusavye inguvu nyinshi  zo gutuza akagwi kahora kanyururuza abantu, kandi ko yasanze muri ako kagwi harimwo n’abakozi b’inzego z’igihugu
 Yamara Focode ivuga  ata kimenyetso ko ivyo vyabaye kandi ko muri rusangi abantu bagirizwa ayo mabi badakurikiranwa ku vyaha baba bakoze
 N’abo bishitse bagafatwa, rimwe na rimwe mbere bakanapfungwa, Focode ivuga ko  mu nyuma baheza bakarekurwa badaciriwe imanza kuri ivyo vyaha
 Focode ivuga ko ivyo bituma kwibaza ko reta irenza uruho rw’amazi kuri bene ayo mabi yo kunyuruza abantu, agasaba umukuru w’igihugu ko imvuga yiwe yojana n’ingiro
 Pacifique Nininahazwe atwara Focode avuga ati: "Ico novuga ko ari ciza gitanguye kubaho, ni ukubona umukuru w'igihugu wenyene atanguye kuvuga ko abarundi banyuruzwa kandi ko mu bantu babanyuruza harimwo abo mu nzego z'umutekano
 "Ku bwacu iyo ni intambwe ikomeye cane
" Muri kahise reta y'Uburundi yavuze ko hari abantu baja hanze y'igihugu harimwo no kuja mu mugwi igwana, amashirahame nka Focode akavuga ko banyurujwe
 Nininahazwe avuga ko adasaba reta kwemera ivyo Focode yatohoje "nk 'ijambo rya bibiriya", asaba umukuru w'igihugu gukoresha inzego z'igihugu gukora amatohoza kuri umwe umwe muri abo bantu  ishirahamwe ryiwe ryemeza ko banyurujwe

