2% mu matora yabaye ku ndwi iheze
 Umugambwe wawukurikiye hafi mu majwi, Unita, waronse 44%
 Unita yari yavuze  iriko iraraba niba yokwanka ivyavuye mu matora
 MPELA, uri ku butegetsi kuva Angola ikironka intahe yo kwikukira mu 1975, yaraneguwe cane kubera urugero runini rw’ubukene n’ubushomeri mu gihugu
 Amajwi yaronse ubu yagabanutse kuva ku 61% mu matora yaheruka mu 2017 mu gihe aya Unita yo yaduze kuva ku 27%
 Umukuru wa Unita, Adalberto Costa Júnior, ku ndwi iheze yaranse ivyavuye mu matora vy’imfatakibanza, avuga ko bidahuye n’ivyo umugambwe wiwe waharuye
 Uburongozi bwa MPLA bwo buja bwatanguye kwigina intsinzi mw’ikoraniro ry’umugambwe ku cicaro cawo ku murwa mukuru, Luanda, nk’uko umunyamakuru  Israel Campos yabibwiye ikiganiro ca BBC Focus on Africa
 MPLA iri ku butegetsi bwa Angola kuva ico gihugu kironse ubwigenge kuri Portugal mu 1975
 MPLA na Unita yarwanye intambara ndende gushika mu 2002 ariko imyaka 20 y’amahoro nta vyinshi yazaniye abanyagihugu nk’uko bari bavyiteze
 Hafi 50% y’abanyagihugu babayeho ku mafaranga adashika ama dorari abiri ($2) ku munsi  n’ubwo igihugu gitunze ibitoro n’amabuye y’agaciro
 Lourenço yabaye umukuru w’igihugu mu 2017 asubiriye uwari amaze imyaka myinshi atwara Amgola, José Eduardo dos Santos
 Kwiyemeza kurwanya ibiturire vyatumye yitandukanya n’umuryango wa Dos Santos n’abawushigikiye, bamwe bakaba baranapfunzwe
  Dos Santos ubwiwe yapfiriye muri Espagne mu kwezi guheze, ku myaka 79
 Ishingurwa ryiwe ryabaye ku wa mungu muri Angola n’ubwo habaye impari za poritike kubera umukobwa wiwe, Tchizé dos Santos, yari yanse ko ashingurwa mu gihugu
 Ariko sentare yo muri Espagne yafashe ingingo ko ikiziga ca Dos Santos gitahanwa kigashikirizwa umupfakazi wiwe

