" Zacharias aratwibutsa ko uguhindura uburyo bwo kubaho ata co bishitseko, bishoboka gutangura kwipimisha no gufata imiti bijanye
 Agira ati:"Mu gihe imbuto z'umugabo zitameze neza, turashobora kubabwira uko umuntu avyifatamwo kugira zibe nziza kandi nyinshi
" Uwo muhinga aravuga kintu ca nyuma kigeramiye abagabo bashaje: Ikibazo kijanye n'akazi ko kurera umwana
