Umugwi w'abanye-Kenya bitwariye reta y'Ubwongereza muri sentare y'agateka ka zina muntu ya Buraya (ECHR) ku mabi bakorewe mu gihe c'ubukoloni
 Muri yo harimwo kwibwa amatongo, n'ubu akirimwamwo n'amakompanyi y'icayi
 Iyo miryango yemeza ko kunanirwa gutorera inyishu ico kibazo mu gutanga impozamarira bihonyanga amasezerano ya Buraya yerekeye agateka ka zina muntu
 Ubushikiranganji bw'imigenderanire bw'Ubwongereza bwabwiye BBC ko "atari vyiza kuvuga ku rubanza ruri mu matohoza"
 Abaserukira imiryango y'aba Talai n'aba Kipsigis, bakomoka mu karere ka Kericho, bavuga ko bagerageje guhura n'umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza ajejwe imigenderanire Liz Truss mu kwezi kwa gatanu mu 2022 ariko ko batavyemerewe
 Umuryango w'aba Talai uvuga ko abawugize birukanywe mu matongo amera mu mitumba ihanamye muri Rift Valley kugira bahashire imirima y'icayi
 Aba Talai baragwanije cane  ko abanye-Buraya baza muri ako karere
 Mu kubahana, umuntu wese wo muri uwo muryango yatwawe ku nguvu mw'ibohero mu karere kagwiriyemwo imibu n'isazi yitwa tse-tse (mouche tse-tse) kegereye ikiyaga ubu citwa Victoria
 Bivugwa ko aho ibintu vyari vyifashe nabi cane ku buryo benshi muri bo bahasize ubuzima, imbanyi z'abagore na zo zaguma zikoroka
 Ibitungwa na vyo vyabo vyarahahoneye ku bwinshi
 Igihe Kenya yikukira mu 1963, abarokotse baciye bava mw'ibohero basubira ku butaka bwa ba sokuru babo
 Ariko ntibigeze babusubirana
 Bavuga ko kuva ico gihe baba mu micungararo y'imirima y'icayi ata ruhusha babifitiye
 Uwuburanira abareze yabwiye radio BBC igisata ca Focus on Africa ko bashaka "impozamarira" muri ako karere ingana na miliyaridi 200 z'amadolari, no "gusaba imbabazi" hanyuma hatangure imigenderanire mishasha ifatiye "ku kwubahana"
 Joel Kimutai Bosek agira ati: "Ayo mabi yatanguye mu 1902 arabandanya gushika 1962
" Yabandanije agira ati: "Turiko turavuga ivyerekeye gutandukanya imiryango
 Abantu bamwe barazimiye ntibasubira kuboneka
 Turiko turavuga ivyerekeye guturira amazu, turiko tuvuga ivyerekeye gukura abantu ku butaka bwa ba sokuru babo
" Abaserukira aba Kipsigis n'aba Talai bavuga ko uko kwitwara ari "intambwe ikomeye" n'"inyishu ku myaka myinshi yari ihaciye hageragezwa ko hoba umubonano na reta y'Ubwongereza imbona nkubone kugira haboneke inyishu ya kivandimwe" uhereye mu 2019
 Ukwitwara muri ECHR ntibisigura ko iyo sentare izoburanisha urwo rubanza, ariko izofata ingingo ko ishobora kurwakira imbere yo gufata ingingo
 Umwe mubakorewe amabi, Kibore Cheruiyot, yari afise imyaka 10 igihe umuryango wiwe wirukanwa ku nguvu, ari kumwe n'abandi bantu bo mu muryango wiwe bimurirwa kure y'aho baba
 Agira ati: "Ubuzima bwari bumeze nabi cane
 Narokotse ku bw'Imana
 Mwenewacu nta mahirwe yagize
 Yakomowe n'inzoka  aca arapfa
 Abantu indwi bo mu muryango wanje na bo barapfuye
" Yabandanije avuga ati: "Hari isazi zitwa tse-tse zarya abantu n'ibikoko, abandi benshi barapfuye
" Ugushingisha urwo rubanza muri ECHR si ubwa mbere ko ivyabashikiye bivugwa ku rwego mpuzamakungu
 Mu 2021, abajejwe amatohoza ya ONU/UN baranditse itangazo berekana "amakenga ku bivugwa vyo kutabazwa no kudatora inyishu ku bakoreye amabi aba Kipsigis n'aba Talai bo mu karere ka Kericho"
