Na  Frances Mao\nBBC News Igihugu ca Korea y’Epfo congeye  kugira urugero rwa mbere ruto kw'isi  rw’abana umugore umwe avyara,  ubu rukaba rwongeye gusubira kumanuka
 Ico gihugu cashitse ubwa mbere musi y’urugero rw’umwana umwe ku mugore mu 2018
 Ariko ku wa gatatu, ibiharuro vyasohowe na reta vyerekanye ko urwo rugero rwamanutse kuri 0,81 - rwasubiye inyuma amanota atatu ugereranije no mu mwaka uheze, ukaba ubaye umwaka ugira gatandatu rwikurikiranya kumanuka
 Ugereranije,   muri rusangi,  urugero mu bihugu bitunze cane kw’isi rungana n’abana 1,6
 Ibihugu bikeneye abana babiri kuri buri mugore n’umugabo - ni urugero rwa 2
1- kugira igitigiri c’abantu bavyo  kigume hamwe, hatarinze kuba abimukira
 Ishami rya ONU riraba ugufashanya mu butunzi n’iterambere OCDE/OECD rivuga ko urugero rwo kuvyara "rwagabanutse cane mu myaka 60 iheze"
 Ariko uwo murindi warakaze  cane muri Korea y’Epfo aho ubunini bw’imiryango bwagabanutse cane mu myaka y’urunganwe itari myinshi cane 
 Mu ntango z’imyaka ya 1970,  abagore muri rusangi bavyara abana bane
 Igihugu aho abakiri bato baguma baba bake gishibora guhura n’ibibazo bitandukanye
 Uretse uburyo biba ngombwa ko bwongerezwa mu kwitaho amagara y’abantu n’iduga ry’amafaranga yo guha abafashe ikiruhuko c’izabukuru, igihugu aho abakiri bato baguma baba bake bisigura ko  n’abashobora gukora  baba bake ivyo na vyo bikagira ingaruka ku butunzi
 Mu 2020 abantu barahagaritswe umutima n’uko ku ncuro ya mbere muri Korea y’Epfo abapfa babaye benshi kurusha abavuka
 Muri iyi myaka ya vuba, imvo zifatiye ku butunzi n’ugutera imbere mu kazi ni zo  zifata ikibanza nyamukuru iyo abantu bashaka gufata ingingo ijanye no kuronka abana, nk’uko abahinga babivuga
 Ku biharuro vyo mu 2021, abahinga bavuze ko ubuzima buzimvye cane, iduga ry’amafaranga y’amazu hamwe n’ingaruka za Covid 19 ari vyo bibuza abantu kugira abana
 Umwihwezo wa Jean MacKenzie BBC Seoul Ikibazo kiriko kirakomera buke buke
 Hamwe igitigiri c’abantu muri Korea y’Epfo coguma kigabanuka, nta bantu bakwiye bazoboneka bo kuguma baduza ubutunzi bw’ico gihugu, ngo bongere binjire mu gisirikare caco
 Abanyeporitike haheze imyaka bazi ko ivyo  bizoshika ariko barananiwe no kubitorera inyishu
 Basutse amafaranga menshui mu kugerageza kwumvisha abantu kugira abana, none n’ubu baguma biyagaza mu mutwe bibaza igituma ivyo bitashobotse
 Amafaranga nta nkeka ko afise ikibanza gikomeye muri ico kibazo
 Kurera abana muri Korea y’Epfo bisaba amafaranga menshi cane, kandi abantu benshi bakiri bato muri ico gihugu bararemerewe n’amafaranga y’amazu
 Ariko kandi hari n’ikibazo c’amahirwe y’akazi
 Abagore muri Korera y’Epfo barize cane, ariko mu buzi si benshi ugereranije n’abagabo
 Ico gihugu kiri mu vya mbere aho hari ubudasa bunini mu mishahara y’abagabo n’abagore kurusha mu kindi gihugu icari co cose gitunze
 Ibikorwa vyo mu rugo no kwitaho abana muri Korea y’Epfo n’ubu biracakorwa  ahanini n’abagore kandi birashika cane ko abagore baheba akazi iyo bavyaye canke na ho ntibasubire gutera imbere mu kazi
 Mu  vy’ukuri abagore benshi ngaha baracahatirwa guhitamwo hagati yo gutera imbere mu kazi canke gushinga umuryango
  Baguma baba benshi mu guhitamwo ko badashaka guheba akazi
 Nk’uko umugore umwe yabimbwiye: “Turi muri yegereyegere yo kuvyara abana”

