 I Kyiv , umunyamabanga w’inama y’umutekano no kwivuna abansi yavuze ko Ukraine ata na hamwe ihuriye n’ubwo bwicanyi
 Ati: “Turafise ibindi bikorwa bihambaye  vyo gutuma abakobwa n’abahungu bacu…FSB niyo yakoze  ivyo none iriko iravuga ko ari umwe muri twebwe yabikoze”, nk’uko yabibwiye television ya Ukraine
 Danilov  yanavuze ko Uburusiya bufise umugambi wo kugaba urukurikirane rw’ibitero imbere mu Burusiya mu ntumbero yo gukabura abarusiya ubu barambiwe no gushigikira intambara
  Urwego rw’Uburusiya rujejwe umutekano (FSB) rwavuze ko  rwamaze kumenya ingene ubwo bwicani bwagenze ruca rwagiriza Ukraine  uruhara rutaziguye
 Ivyo rwavuze vyarasubiwemwo cane na television y’igihugu, abashikiriza ibiganiro bijanye n’amakuru bashigikiye ubutegetsi bwa Moscou nabo bakaba batatevye gusaba ko haba kwihora buno nyene
 Abarusiya basaba kwihora mu gihe Ukraine iriko iritegurira guhimbaza ku wa gatatu imyaka 31 iheze yikuikiye (ironse ubwigenge), bikazohurirana n’uko haheze amezi atandatu Uburusiya buteye ico gihugu
