 Ubwoba bw’uko ibitero vy’Uburusiya bishobora kurushiriza vyatumye abategetsi ba Ukraine babuza ibirori mu gihe igisagara ca Kharkiv naco caciye gishinga amasaha y’umukwabu wo mw’ijoro utangura isaha 10 z’umuhingano mu masaha yo muri Ukraine (isaha indwi z’umutaga kw’isaha mpuzamakungu ya GMT)
 Urwego rw’Uburusiya rujejwe umutekano (FSB) ubu ruvuga ko rwahejeje gutohoza rugasanga Ukraine ifise uruhara rutaziguye muri urwo rupfu
