 Ivuga ko uwo mugore yafashe inzu mu nyubakwa imwe ma madame Dugina kugira agendereze ibijanye n’ubuzima bwiwe
 Urwo rwego rujejwe umutekano ruvuga ko abo bakekwa bakoresha imodoka ya Mini Cooper yari ifise imparati zitatu zidasa
 Uwo akekwa yaciye ahungira muri Estonia  iryo turika rihejeje kuba, nk’uko FSB ivuga
