Umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza ajejwe intwaro yo hagati Priti Patel yashimangiye ko Urwanda ari igihugu kidateye impungenge zo kurungikayo  abarondera ubuhungiro, n'ubwo hari umujenama yaburiye abashikiranganji ko reta y'Urwanda iboreza igufa (ikorera iyicarubozo) abatavuga rumwe nayo
 Iyo mburi yemenyekanye ku wa kabiri, mu rubanza muri sentare nkuru
 Abajijwe kuri iyo mburi, madame Patel yavuze ko iyo  mpanuro yavuye mu kindi gisata ca reta mu gihe ubushikiranganji bw'intwaro yo hagati ari bwo bwari burongoye uwo mugambi
 Yavuze ko ivyo bakorana n'Urwanda vyerekana ko ari igihugu kidateye  impungenge
 Mu mezi aheze, reta y'Ubwongereza yashize ahabona umugambi wo guha bamwe mu binjira mu Bwongereza kuronderayo ubuhingiro baciye mu kiyaga ca Manche itike yo kugenda mu Rwanda utagaruka
 Abashikiranganji basigura ko uwo mugambi uciye miriyoni 120 z'amafaranga y'abangoreza (miriyaridi 150 uyavunje mu mafaranga y'Urwanda)  uzofasha guca intege abantu bajabuka n'abakora urwo rudandazwa rwo kubajabutsa
 Indege yo kujana aba mbere mu barungikwa mu Rwanda   yari yiteguriye guhaguruka mu kwezi kwa gatandatu ariko isiba ku munota wa nyuma abaharanira uburengenzira bwa muntu bamaze kugwanya uwo mugambi mu bucamanza
 Iyo nteguro ubu iri mu mayira abiri gushika nibura mu kwezi kw'icenda igihe sentare ntahinyuzwa izokwihweza uwo mugambi kugira ice urubanza niba uhuye n'amategeko
 Mu rundi rubanza  rwo muri sentare rwabaye muri iyi ndwi, reta yaratsinzwe ku ruhande rumwe kw'igerageza ryo kugumiza mw'ibanga urukurikirane ry'umwihwezo ku Rwanda wagizwe n'umujenama wo mu bushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire
 Uwo mujenama yariko araraba isubiramwo ry'icegeranyo ca reta y'Ubwongereza ku buryo reta y'Urwanda yitwara ku bijanye n'uburenganzira bwa zina muntu
 Hanyuma mu butumwa bwa email yarungikiye abo bakorana ku wa 26 ukwezi kwa kane -indwi zibiri uwo mugambi umaze gushirwa ahabona-  uwo yariko arasubiramwo ico cegeranyo yibaza niba kigaragaza neza uko ibintu vyifashe muri ico gihugu
 Umucamanza Lord Justice Lewis yabwiwe ko uwo mutegetsi yari yanditse muri email yaherekeza umwihwezo wiwe ati: "Ukutavuga rumwe na reta ntivyihanganirwa,  kandi gupfunga   hadakurikijwe amategeko, kuboreza igufa canke mbere no kwica n'uburyo bwemewe bwo kugenzura"
 Abajijwe kuri  ubwo bujenama,  madame Patel yagwaniye umugambi wiwe ashimangira ko Urwanda ari "igihugu ata mpungenge giteye"
 "Muvuga ku vyavuzwe n'abantu bo mu kindi gisata
