Umukenguzamateka wa Amerika yabonanye na William Ruto aherutse gutsinda amatora y’umukuru w’igihugu muri Kenya, yongera abonana na Raila Odinga  yanse ivyavuye mu matora
 Ibiro vy’uwuserukira Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri Kenya vyanditse kuri twitter ko  Chris Coons na William Ruto bavuganye "ugufashanya kw’imikenyuro hagati ya Amerika na Kenya, guteza imbere amahoro n’umutekano mu karere, n’inzira zo gukomeza ubutunzi [bw’ivyo bihugu vyompi]”
 Nk’icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu, William Ruto aracafise ivyo arangura, ariko muri tweet y’ubuserukizi bwa Amerika, nta cavuwe ku ntsinzi ya Ruto canke ku mpari ziyerekeye
 Ubuserukizi bwa Amerika muri Kenya gushika ubu ntiburakeza icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu ku ntsinzi yiwe mu matora
 Ariko inyuma y'aho  umugwi ujejwe amatora muri Kenya utangarije ku wa mbere ko Ruto yatsinze amatora, ubuserukizi bwa Amerika muri Kenya bwarakiriye ko yatangajwe ko ariwe yatsinze amatora hanyuma bukeza umugwi ujejwe amatora n’abanya-Kenya ku matora yabaye mu mahoro no mu nteguro nziza
 Umukenguzamateka Coons yabonanye kandi na Raila Odinga kugira bavugane ”imico myiza ya demokrasi bahuriyeko” nk’uko biri kuri twtter y’ubuserukizi bwa Amerika
   N’aho nyene nta na hamwe havugwa ko ibijanye n’amatora boba babivuganye
 Uwo mukenguzamateka  yabonanye kandi n’umukuru w’igihugu, Uhuru Kenyatta, aho bivugwa ko  kwari "ukumuramutsa”

William Ruto, umukuru w’igihugu yatowe muri Kenya,  yavuze ubwa mbere kuva uwo bahiganywe, Raila Odinga, ahakanye ivyavuye mu matora – amenyesha ko ariko yitegurira gushinga reta
 Raila Odinga ariko araraba inzira zose zitegekanywa n’ibwirizwa nshingiro kugira hateshwe agaciro ivyavuye mu matora
 Ku wa mbere, umukuru w’umugwi ujejwe amatora (IEBC), Wafula Chebukati, yatangaje ko Ruto yatinze amatora ku majwi arenga 50% ku yarenga 48% ya Raila Odinga
 Ariko bane kuri ndwi mu bagize uwo mugwi  bavuze ko badashora kwemenga ivyayavuyemwo
 Odinga yagirije umukuru w’uwo mugwi kwirengagiza ibwirizwa nshingiro n’amategeko mu gutangaza “ibitagira umutwe n’amaguru”
 Ruto yasavye abakozi ba reta bari “bahatiwe kugira uruhande begamira muri poritike gusubira inyuma bakore akazi uko bisanzwe”
 Yemereye abanya-Kenya ko akazi ka reta kazokorwa ata nkunzi, hatisunzwe aho umuntu yegamiye muri poritike
 Ashikiriza ijambo abo mu runani rwiwe, Ruto yabasavye “gukura icigwa ku  banya-Kenya bo barangije ikibazo”
 Yagarutse ku “kwigina kuriko kuraba mu gihugu cose”  nk’ugushaka kuvuga ko abanyagihugu bemeye ivyavuye mu matora
 Akanya gato avuze ivyo, abo mu runani kwa Raila Odinga bashimangiye urugamba rwabo rwo kurondera ko ivyavuye mu matora y’umukuru w’igihugu bigwizwa n’ubusa
 Martha Karua, yitoje hamwe na Raila Odinga ku giti co kuba icegera ciwe abaye umukuru w’igihugu, yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru urunani rwabo, Azimio La Umoja, ruhejeje kubonana ati:  “Ku kibazo c’amatora, iyacu n’intsinzi ibaye irigizwa inyuma, ariko izotaha iwacu”
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije abanywanyi biwe, Ruto ntaco  yavuze ko vyashikirijwe na Raila Odinga igihe yamenyesha ko yanse ivyavuye amatora
  Ibintu vyasubiye kuba ibisanzwe muri Migori, mu burengero bwa Kenya
 Ni  kamwe mu turere twabayemwo imyiyerekano irimwo intureka  inyuma y’aho umukuru w’umugwi ujejwe amatora amariye gutangaza ko William Ruto ariwe mukuru w’igihugu yatowe ku wa mbere ku mugoroba
 N’akarere k’abashigikiye uwo bahiganwa, Raila Odinga, yanse ivyavuye muri ayo matora
 Jeffers Omondi, w’imyaka 24, mu gitondo yariko arateka ikawa yo kugurisha kw’ibarabara nk’uko yahora
 Yavuze ko anezerewe n’ukubona hatekanye inyuma y’intureka yo ku wa mbere
 Ariko yavuze ko ashigikiye ingingo ya Odinga yo kuja muri sentare avuga ko ubutungane butegerezwa gukora
 Lillian Akinyi, w’imyaka 48, we agurisha ibirato
 Biteye kubiri na benshi mu bashigikiye Odinga, we avuga ko ivyo kwanka ivyavuye mu matora bikwiye kurangira
 Ati: “Abana bacu bakeneye gusubira kw’ishure, kandi dushaka gusubira mu bikorwa vyacu vya minsi yose
 Yongera ati: "Odinga arakwiye kureka ico kibazo kikarangira”

Inyuma y’intureka yakurikiye impari z’amatora y’umukuru w’igihugu mu 2007, William Ruto yagirijwe na sentare mpuzamakungu mpanavyaha ICC/CPI gukokeza ivyaha bikorewe zina muntu
 Ruto niwe aheruka gutangazwa ko yatsinze amatora ya prezida wa Kenya
 Ico gihe Ruto yagirijwe kwica, kwangaza no kuburabuza – ivyo vyose akaba yarabihakanye
 Vyavugwa ko yari kizigenza mu gutunganya umugambi wo gutera abanywanyi ba Party of National Unity muri Rift Valley
 Mu gihe urubanza rwariko ruraba, ku bw’abashikirizamanza, bamwe mu bari kuba ivyabona/abatangabuhamya barishwe, abandi baraburwa irengero canke arakosora ivyo yari yavuze
 Abunganira Ruto bavuze ko ivyabona b’ubushikirizamanza babwirwa ivyo bavuga canke bagahabwa agashirukabutse kugira bavuge
 Amaherezo urubanza rwahavuye rubura ifatiro, sentare ivuga ko ata vyemeza bikwiye kugira rubandanye, ariko yanka kweza Ruto
 Umwe mu bacamanza yavuze ko urubanza rwagenze nabi kuko “habaye ukwishuka mu bijanye n’amasura hamwe n’ukwivanga kubabaje kwa poritike”
 Abacamanza ba ICC bavuze ko urwo rubanza rushobora gusubira kwugururwa hamwe hoboneka ibindi vyemeza
 Ariko, hari akagoborandya muri iyi harabaye
 Uwahora ari umushingwamanza aburanira Ruto, Karim Khan QC, ubu niwe mushikirizamanza wa ICC, rero kuzana ibishasha ku wahoze ari umukiriya wiwe vyojana sentare  mu karere itazi – bikazana kandi ibibazo bishasha kuri ICC na Ruto

Raila Odinga yahakanye ivyavuye mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu yabaye muri Kenya mu ndwi iheze
 Mw'itangazo yasomye imbere vy'ibinyamakuru, Odinga yavuze ko azoca mu nzira zose zemewe n'amategeko kugira ivyavuye mu matora bibe impfagusa
 Ku wa mbere umukuru w'umugwi ujejwe amatora yatangaje ko ayo matora yatsinzwe na Willian Ruto ku majwi 50,49% ku ri 48,85% ya Raila Odinga
 Gusa imbere y'uko ivyavuye mu matora bitangazwa  , bane kuri ndwi bagize umugwi ujejwe amatora batangaje ko badashobora "kwemanga ivyayavuyemwo kubera umwijima waranze intambwe  ya nyuma yo gusuzuma amajwi"
 Mr Odinga yagirije umukuru w'umugwi ujejwe amatora, Wafula Chebukati "kwirengagiza vyeruye ibwirizwa nshingiro"
 Yavuze ati: "Turiyamirije twivuye inyuma ivyavuye mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu"
 Odinga yari amaze kwanka ivyavuye mu matora abiri yaheruka, mu 2017 sentare ikaba yaremeje ikirego ciwe amatora arasubirwamwo
 Imbere y'uko Raila Odinga ashikiriza aho ahagaze, bane kuri ndwi bagize umugwi ujejwe amatora bari bahaye ikiganiro abamenyeshamakuru kugira basigure igituma bavyanse
 Bavuze ko umukuru w'umugwi, Wafula Chebukati, yabakumiriye hageze gutangaza ivyavuye mu matora, hanyuma atangaza ibiharuro birimwo amakosa kandi "bitagira umutwe n'amaguru"
 Icegera ciwe Julia Cherera yavuze ko uteranije ivyo kw'ijana Chebukati yatangaje utora 100,1% , ariko hari abavuga ko ivyo vyatewe no kwihenda mu kuduza igiharuro kiza inyuma y'agakwabu
 N'aho biri uko, ibihugu bitandukanye birimwo Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika vyakeje abanya-Kenya uburyo bitwaye mu matora binakeza uwayatsinze, William Ruto
 Abakuru b'ibihugu bitandukanye ba Afrika nabo bakeje William Ruto ku ntsinzi yaraye atahanye
 Raila Odinga w'imyaka 77 bwari ubugira gatanu yitoza mu kibanza c'umukuru w'igihugu
 William Ruto w'imyaka 55, yari asanzwe ari icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu, Uhuru Kenyatta, arangije ikiringo ca kabiri c'imyaka itanu, akaba atari arekuriwe gusubira kwitoza nk'uko amategeko ya Kenya abitegekanya
 Muri aya matora ariko, Uhuru Kenyatta yahisemwo gushigikira uwo batahora bavuga rumwe, Raila Odinga

Hagati mu kwezi kwa Myandagaro (8) ingabo z’Uburundi zinjiye icese ku butaka bwa Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo mu rwego rw’ishirahamwe rya Afrika y’Ubuseruko, EAC
 Ku bwa Lieutenant Elongo Marc, umuvugizi wa secteur operationel Sokola 2 muri Sud Kivu, ingabo z’Uburundi zinjiye “icese mu gitondo co kuri uyu wa mbere”
 Yabwiye BBC Gahuzamiryango ko zinjiriye mu karere ka Uvira ubu zikaba ziri ahitwa Ruberizi
 Lt Elongo ntiyashimye kuvuga igitigiri c’ingabo z’Uburundi zinjiye uko kingana ariko yemeza ko ari  “igitigiri gifadika” kuko haje “contingent yose” n’ibikoresho  “ingabo zose zikenera”
 Imihari idaharanira inyungu za poritike aho muri RD Congo yavuze ko ingabo z'Uburundi haheze amezi zarinjiye kurwanya imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho y'abarundi nka Red Tabara
 Uwo mugwi nawo nyene kuva mu mwaka uheze wemeza ko ugwana n'ingabo z'Uburundi mu karere ka Uvira
 Ariko Uburundi na RD Congo vyompi vyagumye bibihakana
 Mu kwezi kwa kane abakuru b’ibihugu vy’ishirahamwe rya Afrika y’Ubuseruko, EAC, bumvikanye ko hashingwa ingabo zoja gufasha iza Congo kurwanya imigwi yose yitwaje ibigwanisho iri mu buseruko bw’ico gihugu
 Ariko reta ya Congo yavuze ko ata ngabo z'Urwanda izokwemera ko zirungikwayo
 RD Congo yagiriza Urwanda gushigikira umugwi wa M23
 Urwanda rurabihakana ahubwo narwo rukagiriza ingabo za RD Congo gukorana n'abitwaje ibigwanisho ba FDLR bagwanya reta y'Urwanda
 Iciyumviro c'ingabo za EAC cizwe vyihuta n'abakuru b'ibihugu aho umugwi witwaje ibigwanisho wa M23 wongereye kuvyura ibitero mu buseruko bwa Congo mbere ukigarurira ibice bimwe bimwe birimwo igisagara ca Bunagana
 Uwo mugwi wavuze ko udatewe ubwoba n'izo ngabo
 N'umugwi w'abarundi wa Red Tabara wavuze ko kurungika izo ngabo atari yo nyishu y'ibibazo
 Lt Elongo yavuze ko ingabo ziva mu bindi bihugu nka Kenya, Uganda  na Tanzania zitarinjira, kandi ngo zinjiye zizoja mu bindi bice vy’ubuseruko bwa RD Congo
 Ariko iza Uganda zo niyo zisanzwe kuva mu mwaka uheze mu bufatanye mu kurwanya umugwi ADF uturuka muri Uganda nyene
 Lt Elongo yavuze ko ingabo za RD Congo n’izo z’Uburundi ubu zigiye gutangura  imyiteguro kugira zitangure kurwanya iyo migwi yaba iyo abanye-Congo nka za Mai Mai canke  iyituruka mu mahanga nka Red Tabara na FNL Bamwe mu banye-Congo nka Dr Denis Mukwege, umuganga w’umunye-Congo yatsindiye agashimwe k’amahoro kitiriwe Nobel, na Martin Fayulu, indongozi y'abatavuga rumwe na reta nta cizere kinini bafitiye izo ngabo z'akarere
 Muri Congo hasanzwe ibihumbi vy'ingabo za ONU - Monusco - zihamaze imyaka irenga 20 nazo nyene zifise inshingano zo gufasha ingabo za reta kurwanya imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho no gukingira abanyagihugu
 Ariko iyo migwi n'ubu yagumye ihungabanya umutekano
 Bigereranywa ko uwo mutekano muke umaze guhitana abantu barenga miriyoni 5, abandi benshi gusumba barateshwa izabo

Ubushinwa buriko buragira imyimenyerezo  ya gisirikare y'akataraboneka mu micungararo ya Taiwan, igihugu bufata ko kiri mu bigize Ubushinwa
 Iyo myimenyerezo yatangujwe mu kwishura ku rugendo umukuru w'inama nshingamateka ya Amerika, Nancy Pelosi, yagize kuri iryo zinga, irimwo gutera misile mu kiyaga no kwinjira mu kirere ca Taiwan
 Kuva mu myaka irenga 20, imishamirano hagati y'Ubushinwa na Taiwan yagumye yongerekana, ku buryo kuba Ubushinwa bushobora gutera iryo zinga ari abantu bari kurushi boba babona ko bidashoboka
 Mu gihe Ubushinwa bwotera Taiwan, intambara y'ibihugu bitanganya inguvu yoca yaduka, n'ukuvuga intambara aho  kimwe muri ivyo bihugu gifise inguvu z'umurengera za gisirikare gusumba ico bahanganye
 N'intambara turiko turabona ubu hagati y'Uburusiya na Ukraine, kandi yatweretse ko ukutanganya inguvu ata co bisa bisana n'ibibera ku rubuga rw'intambara
 Ibintu vyoba ibindi mu gihe Ubushinwa bwotera Taiwan? Ubushinwa bubamwo abantu imiriyaridi 1
4 ku miliyoni 24
5 z'abo muri Taiwan, bukoresha amahera angana incuro 13 mu gisirikare ugereranije n'umubanyi wabwo, burusha kure, ufatiye ku gitigiri c'abasirikare, ibikoresho hamwe n'ibigwanisho
 Mu gihe Taiwan izi neza ko ata nguvu ifise, yaciye itora "amayeri y'ikinyogoto"
 Cumvise ko kigeramiwe, ikinyogoto gica gishinga utwoya twaco dushinze nk'uducumu kugira kibuze igikoko gishaka kukirya kucegera
 "Ububabare bwo guhonyora kuri utwo ducumu tw'ikinyogoto, ni yo nzitizi ya mbere ibuza ko kiribwa", nk'uko bisigurwa n'ikinyamakuru Taipei Times
 Mu gihe ariko ico gikoko ciyemeje gutera ico kinyogoto, kirahabonera kikaruhira guheba
 Amayeri ya Taiwan ahagaze kuri ivyo, binemezwa mu cegeranyo co kwivuna umwansi citwa Quadrennial Defence Review co mu 2021
 "Kurinda umwansi ku nkengera birabana, kumuterera mu mazi, kumusamburira ahegereye inkengera hamwe  no kumuzimanganiriza ku biraro", ivyo ni vyo ico cegeranyo kivuga
 Mu kugwana intambara n'ababarusha inguvu, Taiwan ntishira imbere kurondera indege karuhariwe n'amato yibira azimvye, ahubwo gukwiragiza ibigwanisho vyo kwikingira biguma bihindura ibibanza kandi binyegeje, nka misile zirasa indege n'izirasa amato
 Zeno Leoni, umuhinga mu vyo kwivuna abansi n'imigenderanire hagati y'Ubushinwa n'Uburaya akora kuri Kaminuza King's College y'i Londres, yaragize umwihwezo kuri izo mpome zitatu zituma Taiwan igira amayeri y'ikinyogoto
 Mu nyandiko yerekeye uburyo bwo kwikingira bwa Taiwan yashizwe ahabona mu kinyamakuru The Conversation, yasiguye ati:"Uruhome rw'inyuma rugizwe n'iperereza no gutata mu ntumbero yo kwihweza nimba igisirikare kiryamiye amajanja
" Kuva mu myaka irenga mirongo ibiri, Taiwan yarateguye uburyo bwo kugabisha hakiri kare, kugira yikingire ibitero vya bukwi na bukwi itari yiteze vy'Ubushinwa
 Gutyo, Ubushinwa "bwotegerezwa gutangura gutera bukoresheje misile zishika ahantu hagereranye hamwe n'ibitero vyo mu kirere mu gusambura ivyuma vya 'radar' , ibibuga vy'indege hamwe n'inkoho zitera misile vya Taiwan
" Mu kwishura ku gitero nk'ico, uruhome rwo hagati rw'ikinyogoto rugizwe no kugomora ingabo zigwanira mu mazi kugira habe ibitero vyo mu kiyaga bafashijwe n'indege z'intambara bahawe na Reta zunze Ubumbwe za Amerika, nk'uko uwo muhinga abivuga
 Ubwato buto buto kandi bunyaruka butera misile bufashijwe na za kajugujugu z'intambara hamwe n'inkoho zitera misile ziri ku butaka, bishobora kugerageza kubuza amato y'abashinwa gushika ku butaka bwa Taiwan
 Canke ko mu gihe boramuka bashitse ku butaka bwa Taiwan, bazibonerako mu kubura abasirikare benshi n'ibikoresho
 Leoni asigura ati: "Uko Taiwan imeze hamwe n'abanyagihugu bayo ni vyo bigize uruhome rugira gatatu rwo kwikingira
" Imisozi ya Formose ihanamye cane, inkengera z'ikiyaga zoroshe kwururukirako hamwe n'igice kinini cubatswemwo, biha amahigwe abazoba bariko barigwanako, kandi bishobora gutuma abateye bahatakariza ibintu vyinshi
 Ikindi, mu gihe abasirikare b'Ubushinwa baruta kure aba Taiwan incuro 12 mu bwinshi, bafise kandi abarenga imiliyoni n'igice bahamagarwa iyo bakenewe (réservistes) bokwinjira mu ntambara mu gihe ingabo z'Ubushinwa zoba ziteye ico gihugu
 Ibigwanisho bihindagura ibibanza, bikoreshwa mu buryo butandukanye kandi vyoroshe kunyegeza ni vyo vyoba kirumara ku ruhome rwa gatatu, nk'uko vyagaragaye muri Ukraine mu gukoresha misile ngendanwa za Javelin na Stinger zabiciye biracika ku ndege n'ibimodoka bitamenwa vy'Uburusiya
 Mu kwezi kwa gatanu, Perezida Joe Biden yatangaje abantu benshi mu kuvuga ko igihugu ciwe "cafashe ingingo" yo gutabara Taiwan, n'aho mu nyuma yisubiyeko mu kuvuga ko atacahindutse ku "mikenyuro iteye amadidane"
 Iyo ngingo ntitumbereye gusa guca intege Ubushinwa ngo ntibutere Taiwan, inagamije kubuza Taiwan gutangaza ko yikukiye (Ubushinwa bwaragabishije ko buzoyitera niyabikora), mu gihe idashigikiwe muri ico gikorwa na Amerika
 Bamwe mu bagize inama nshingamateka ya Amerika barasavye ko hoba impinduka aho ico gihugu gihagaze mu "gushira ahabona imikenyuro" yo guca intege Ubushinwa, bubandanya bwotsa igitutu Taiwan, no kwongereza ingabo muri ako karere
 Uko biri kose, abantu bari ku rushi ni bo bacibaza ko Amerika yorera amaboko mu gihe Ubushinwa bwotera Taiwan
 Ukwerekana inguvu za gisirikare kw'Ubushinwa biratera uruhagarara ku buzima bwa misi yose bwa Taiwan, abantu ahanini birabababaje cane gusumba kubatera ubwoba
 Uruja n'uruza rwo mu mazi hamwe n'amakompanyi y'indege vyaragize ibibazo bikomeye, aho amato aguma ahagaze ku bivuko, indege na zo zasivya ingendo inyuma y'aho Ubushinwa buburije kuja mu nkengera ry'iryo zinga kubera imyimenyerezo ya gisirikare yariko irahabera

