Umukuru w’igihugu ca Ukraine Volodymir Zelensky yasavye ibihugu vya Bulaya vyose  kwankira abarusiya bose kugendera uwo mugabane -ivyo Uburusiya bwakengereye cane
 Zelensky yabariye ikinyamakuru Washington Post ko ‘’abarusiya bakwiye kuba kw’isi ya bonyene gushika bahinduye ingendo’’
 Such a ban, he argued, would be more effective than the current sanctions, which bar Russian airlines and officials linked to the Kremlin
 Avugako iyo ngingo yogira akamaro kurusha ibihano biriho ubu vyankira  indege z’Uburusiya hamwe n’abarongozi bacuditse n'ubutegetsi bw'Uburusiya kuja i Buraya
 Abarusiya baracaronka impusha zo kwinjira (visa) mu bihugu vuya Buraya na Amerika
 Akamo Zelensky yateye  gashobora kuronka abagashigikira bake kubera Uburusiya -naho buri mu bihano-  busanganywe imigenderanire muvyo urudandazwa kandi abarusiya babandanya bakirwa mu bikunzwe gufatirwamo akaruhuko nka Misiri , Turkiya na Arabiya Saoudite
 Ariko ku musi wa kabiri , umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Estonia Kaja Kallas   yanditse kuri twitter ati: "Hagarika guha visa ingenzi z'abarusiya
 Kuja gutembera i Buraya ni ibakwe, si uburenganzira bwa  zina muntu
" Mu kwezi guheze , umushikiranganji wa Latvia ajejwe imigenderanire  Edgars Rinkevics yabariye ikinyamakuru Politico gikorera kuri internet ko ibihugu vya Bulaya bikwiye kugabanya visa zihabwa abarusiya, zemererwe gusa abafise imvo zotuma bahura n'akaga
 No ku musi wa mbere igihugu kibanyi mu uraruko, Finlande,  carashigikiye kugabanya guha impusha ababuriya
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Finlande, Sanna Marin,  yabariye  radio-television  y’igihugu YLE ko ‘’ bidakwiye ko Uburusiya butogira gutera  intambara y'agasomborotso n'akaga i  Buraya, hanyuma ngo abarusiya babandanye kubaho ubuzima busanzwe, baja i Buraya, baja gutemebera"
 Ibihugu vya Estonia na Finlande vyitezwe ko bizoshikana ikibazo ca visa  mu nama ya vuba y’abashikiranganji bajewe imigenderanire
 Umuvugizi wa Vladmir Putin,  Dmitry Peskov,  yiyamirije ivyasabwe na  Zelensky avugako "ata bundi buryo bwo kubifata atari nabi cane"
 Yavuze ati :"Kugerageza mu buryo ubwari bwo bwose guharira ivomo (gushira mu kato) abarusiya n'Uburusiya, ni umugambi ataco ushobora gushikako
 " Visa Schengen yemerera uwuyihawe kuguma mu bihugu vy'Ishirahamwe rya Buraya iminsi 90 ku mvo zo gutembera canke z'ivyashara
 Umuntu ashobora gutembera uko ashatse mu bihugu 26 bigize Schengen muri ico kiringo -ako karere kakaba kagizwe n'ibihugu 22 hiyongerako Islande,  Norvege, Ubuswise, na Liechtenstein
 Abarisiya rero n'ubu baracashobora gutembera mu bihugu vya Buraya n'ubwo ata ndege zibajanayo zitaziguye
 Ariko abarusiya bari ku rutonde rw’ibihano vy'Uburengerazuba (Buraya na Amerika) - bagizwe ahanini n'abatunzi ruhebwa n’abategetsi bacuditse na Vladimir Putin- ntibemerewe
 Ibitero vy'Uburusiya kuri UKraine  vyatanguye  itariki 24 z'ukwezi kwa kabiri  vyatumye ibihugu vy'iburengarazuba bibufatira  ibihano vyongera bituma abarusiya baharugwa mu bihumbi baja mu mahanga
 Barimwo abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi, ariko hari n’abandi batafise ivyo baharanira muri poritike bashimye kuronderera ubuzima hanze y’Uburusiya
 Zelensky yavuzeko ibihano bihambaye ari ukwugara imbibe kubera Aburusiya buriko barigarurira ubutaka bw’ikindi guhugu
 Yari amaze kwiyamiriza ko ibihugu vya Bulaya vyananiwe kureka kugurira gaze n’igitoro mu Burusiya, ari navyo bibufasha kugwana iyo ntambara yo muri Ukraine
 Igitero c'Uburusiya kuri Ukraine kwatumye abantu baharugwa mu bihumbi bicwa gituma miriyoni z'abanya-Ukraine bahunga igihugu ahanini baja  muri Pologne no mu bindi bihugu vya Buraya vy'ishirahamwe vya Buraya vyegeranye

Umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU/UN, Antonio Guterres yashimiye abanye Kenya kuba barabungabunze amahoro mu gihe c'amatora
 Mw'itangazo, umunyamabanga mukuru yashimiye akanama kajejwe gutunganya amatora n'abategetsi ba Kenya mu kuba karitwararitse ko abitavye amatora bakora ico gikorwa bafitiye uburenganzira mu mwidegemvyo, nk'uko biri mw'ibwirizwa shingiro
 Yasavye abanyepolitike n'abatoye gutekana no kwigumya igihe bakirindiriye ko iharurwa ry'ivyavuye mu matora rirangira
 Abantu 65
4 kw'ijana y'abiyandikishije gutora bashika imiliyoni 22
1 ni bo bitavye ico gikorwa itariki 9 z'ukwezi kw'umunani 2022
 Akanama kajejwe gutegura amatora ntikaratanga ibiharuro ntabanduka vy'abitavye amatora
 Ibiharuro vyerekana ko abitavye amatora bagabanutse ugereranije n'ayo mu mwaka wa 2017 aho abashika 80% z'abari biyandikishije gutora imiliyoni 19 ari bo bitavye ico gikorwa
 Bigaragara ko icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu William Ruto n'umunyepolitike atavuga rumwe na reta Raila Odinga ariko ashigikiwe na prezida Uhuru Kenyatta, ari bo baza imbere mu biharuro
 Gushika ubu akanama kajejwe gutegura amatora karamaze kwegeranya ibice 99% vy'amajwi
 Ako kanama kavuga ko kadashobora kugira ico gashikirije imbere y'uko kegeranya ibiharuro vyose 
 Ako kanama kandi gafise imisi indwi ngo kabe kashikirije ivyavuye muri ayo matora

Umushikiranganji wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire avuga ko, mu rugendo yakoze mu Rwanda no muri Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo, yahaye ubutumwa bumwe abategetsi  b'ivyo bihugu vompi
 Mu kiganiro n'abamenyeshamakuru  mu kurangiza urugendo rwiwe mu Rwanda, ari kumwe n'umuhsikiranganji w'ico gihugu ajejwe imigenderanire, Vincent Biruta, Antony Blinken yavuze ko abategetsi b'ibihugu vyompi  yababwiye ko "gushigikira canke gukorana n'umugwi witwaje ibigwanisho uwariwo wose mu buseruko bwa Congo bishira mu akaga abahaba n'amaragamo y'akarere"
 Yavuze ko buri gihugu gitegerezwa kwubahiriza ubutavogerwa bw'ikindi gihugu
 Blinken yabonanye n'umukuru w'Urwanda, Paul Kagame,  yamenyesheje ko bavuganye ku cegeranyo 'co kwizera' kivuga ko Urwanda rushigikiye umugwi M23 ugwaniriza reta ya Congo mu buseruko bw'ico gihugu hamwe n'uko Urwanda rufise ingabo muri ako karere
 Ivyo ni navyo Congo yagiriza Urwanda
 Ariko kandi uwo  mutegetsi wo muri reta  ya Amerika yavuze kandi ko yumva impungene z'Urwanda ku bibazo vy'umutekano warwo harimwo n'uko  ingabo za Congo n'iza ONU zikorana n'umugwi FDLR
 Ati "Turazi kandi ko Urwanda rutewe impungene mu buryo bwumvikana  n'amajambo y'urwanko atota abavuga ikinyarwanda muri Congo"
 Blinken yavuze ko Amerika izokomeza kwiyamiriza bene ayo majambo kandi ko yateye intege reta ya prezida Tshisekedi nayo kubikora
 Yavuze ko ico akuye muri urwo rugendo ari  uko abakuru b'ibihugu vyompi biyemeje kubandanya bavugana kuri ivyo bibazo, anashima utwirogoro tw'abategetsi ba Angola na Kenya mu gufasha gutora inyishu y'ikibazo ca Congo kimaze guhitana abantu barenga "miriyoni zitanu abandi benshi kurusha  bagateshwa izabo"
 Antony  Blinken yavuze kandi ko mu biganiro na prezida Kagame harimwo n'ikibazo ca Paul Rusesabagina
 Blinken yavuze ko yashikirije impungene za Amerika z'uko hatakozwe ibikenewe vyose kugira Rusesabagina acirirwe urubanza rutagira akanenge
 Rusesabagina yaba muri Amerika mu buryo bwemwe n'amategeko mu 2020 yisanze ageze mu Rwanda mu buryo yavuze ko kwabaye ukumuyuruza
 Rusesabagina azwi cane muri film Hotel Rwanda ku ruhara yagize mu gukiza  abatutsi muri jenocide yo mu 1994 mu mwaka uheze yaciriwe gupfungwa imyaka 25 yagirizwa ivyaha vy'iterabwoba
 Umushikiranganji w'Urwanda ajejwe imigenderanire Vincent Biruta yavuze ko Rusesabagina  yaciriwe urubanza "hisunzwe amateko y'urwanda na mpuzamakungu" kandi ko asaba abo bafashanya kwubahiriza  ubucamanza n'inzego z'Urwanda
 Kuri ico kibazo, Antony Blinken yavuze ko ata vyinshi avuga ku co bakivuganyeko n'umukuru w'Urwanda ariko ko Amerika izobandanya kugikurikirana

Gushika ubu abanya-Kenya ntibaremanya uwugiye kuzoba umukuru w'igihugu wabo mushasha  inyuma y'iminsi hafi itatu kuva batoye
 Umukuru w'umugwi ujejwe amatora Wafula Chebukati yasavye abanyagihugu kwihangana no kutaterwa umutima uhagaze n'ubudasa bw'ibiva mu matora bishikirizwa n'ibinyamakuru bitandukanye
 Kimwe kimwe muri ivyo binyamakuru gikora ibiharuro vyaco n'iminwe gifatiye ku biva mu biro 46
000 vy'amatora
 Ariko umugwi w'igihugu ujejwe amatora niwo wonyene uzotangaza uwatsinze
 Gushika ubu ibinyamakuru vyerekana ko  babiri baza imbere mu majwi -Raila Odinga na William Ruto - begeranye cane mu majwi
 Umukuru w'umugwi w'igihugu ujejwe amatora (IEBC), Chebukati ati: "Nta mutima uhagaze mukwiye guterwa n'ubudasa mubona ku mboneshakure z'ibinyamakuru
 "Ivyo zerekana biva hamwe [ku rubuga rw'umugwi], gusa buri kinyamakuru kibikora ukwaco"
 Yavuze ko ibiharuro vyose bimaze guteranywa ibizovamwo bizoba bisa
 Kimwe kimwe mu binyamakuru  giteranya ibiharo ku muvuduko utandukanye n'uwo ikindi kandi kigahitamwo ibiro vy'amatora mu rutonde rutandukanye
 Kuri IEBC, uretse guteranya ibivuye mu matora, abo muri uwo mugwi bategerezwa guhinyuza kimwe kimwe - ikindi gikorwa gitwara umwanya cane
 Abajejwe amatora ubu bariko baragereranya ivyo umugwi waronse mu buryo bw'amafoto bivuye mu biro vy'amatora n'urupapuro nyene izina rw'ivyavuye mu matora rushikirizwa imbona nkubone ikigo c'igihugu kijejwe gushira hamwe ivyavuye mu matora ku murwa mukuru Nairobi
 Aho n'ukugira basuzume ko ivyarungitswe muri ubwo buryo bubiri bihura ari nayo mpamvu nyamukuru ibintu biteba cane
 N'ingendo ao  kuva mu bice bimwe bimwe vy'igihugu uja ku murwa mukuru Nairobi nazo zishobora kuba zaratebeje ibintu
 Hari abo biteye umutima uhagaze mu gihugu kuko amatati y'amatora muri kahise yatumye haba intureka irimwo b'ubwicanyi canke gufuta ivyavuye mu matora
 Inyuma y'amatora yo mu 2007, abantu nibura 1
200 barishwe abarenga 600
000 barahunga ingo zabo kubera abavuze ko amatora yibwe
 Mu  2017, sentare ntahinyuzwa yarafuse ivyavuye mu matora aca arasubirwamwo biturutse ku mvo z'ibikoresho
 Ubub rero abajejwe amatora bari ku gitutu c'uko atacosubira kwononekara
 Ku murindi uguharura biriko biragendako, ibinyamakuru vyo muri Kenya bishobora guheza guteranya ivy'imfatakibanza imbere y'uko umunsi uhera kuri uyu wa kane
 Habonetse uwo bigaragara ko yatahukanye intsinzi,  ukwigina intsinzi birashobora guca bitangura ubwo nyene
 Ariko umugwi ujejwe amatora wonyene niwo ushobora gushikiriza uwatsinze umaze guhinyuza ivyavuye mu matora
 Umugwi ujejwe amatora ufise iminsi indwi kugira ushikirize ivyayaavuyemwo uhereye ku munsi yabereyeko
 Kugira umuntu atsinde amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu ategerezwa kuronka: Bitagenze uko haca haba amatora agira kabiri, ategerezwa kuba itariki 8 z'ukwezi kw'icenda nk'uko amategeko abivuga

Ingorane z'ibikoresho n'ubuhinga bwo gusuzuma umwidondoro w'abatora  butakoze neza mu bice bimwe  vy'igihugu  vyatovye amatora ahanini yabaye mu mahoro muri Kenya
 Amatora vyari bitegekanijwe ko arangira isaha cumi n'imwe z'umugoroba mu masaha yo muri Kenya ariko aho yatanguye atevye amasaha yongerejwe
 Ayo matora abaye inyuma y'imyiyamamazo ikomeye yashingiye ahanini ku bibazo vy'ubuzima buguma buzimba, ku bushomeri hamwe n'ibiturire
 Abaza imbere mu mahirwe yo gutsindira intebe y'umukuru w'igihugu ni uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere Raila Odinga hamwe n'uwusanzwe ari icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu Williamn Ruto
 Abanya-Kenya bari baramutse kandi batora inama nshingamateka nshasha hamwe n'abarongoye inzego z'intara n'utundi turere tw'intwaro  mu gihugu
 Mu gihe c'isaha 10 zo ku mugoroba, umugwi ujejwe amatora uvuga ko hari hamaze gutora abantu 12
065
803 kuri 22
120
458 biyandikishije, ni ukuvuga 56
16% (kw'ijana)  hatarimwo abatoreye ku mpapuro
 Umwe mu bajejwe amatora mu ntara ya Nyeri yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ko urugero rw'abitavye amatora rwabaye ruto agereraranije no mu 2017
 Guhurara amajwi vyari bitegekanijwe amatora arangiye, amajwi y'umukuru w'igihugu akaba ari yo aharurwa ubwa mbere
 Igihe yaja gutora muri Kibera, Raila Odinga yakiriwe n'isinzi ry'abantu muri ako karere afisemwo abanywanyi benshi cane ku murwa mukuru Nairobi
 Odinga ntaco yabwiye abamenmyeshamakuru, ariko umugore wiwe, Ida Odinga, yavuze ko "anezerejwe cane n'amatora"
 Igihe Ruto yatora mu gisagara ca Eldoret muri Rift Valley, yiyemeje kuzokwemera ibivuye mu matora
 Yabwiye BBC ati : " Nibaza ko ubwa mbere muri kahise ka demokrasi ishingiye ku migambwe myinshi muri Kenya, abakandida bose biyemeje kuzokwubahiriza ibizova mu matora"
 Impari ziturutse ku  vyavuye mu matora  mu 2007 vyatumye haba intureka yamaze amayinga, igwamwo abantu bashika 1
200,  ituma abandi bashika 600
000 bahunga ingo zabo
 Ugutora hari hamwe hamwe kwatanguye gutevye harimwo muri Westlands  ku murwa mukuru Nairobi
 No mu karere ko kw'ibahari i Mombasa no bice bimwe bimwe vyo mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko habaye ugucererwa
 Mu karere ka Kakamega, mu burengero, zimwe mu mashine zifata amakanda y'intoke vyanse ko zikora
 Ariko umugwi ujejwe amatora wavuze ko mu gihugu cose imashini zanse gukora ari 200 ku 46
000 
 Ivyavuye mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu mu 2017 vyarafuswe na sentare ntahinyuzwa ku ngingo y'uko umugwi ujejwe amatora utari wakurikije amategeko mu gukoresha ubuhinga bwo kurungika amajwi kuva ku bibanza vy'amatora
 Ico gihe amatora yaciye asubirwamwo atsindwa na Uhuru Kenyatta ariko Odinga yanka kuyitaba- ico gihe niwe yari uwuza imbere mu batavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi
 Umukuru w'umugwi ujejwe amatora, Wafula Chebukati, yagumye yizeza abanya-kenya ko ubu ibintu bizogenda neza

