Israel yishe uwundi mutegetsi mukuru w’inyeshamba zo mu muhari w’abarwanyi ba Palestina, bazwi nka Palestinian Islamic Jihad, mu gihe ibitigiri vy’abagwa muri ibi bitero vy’indege muri Gaza
 Abana batandatu hamwe n’abarwanyi batari bake ba PIJ  - harimwo intwazangabo Khaled Mansour na Tayseer Jabari – bari mu banya-Palestina 32 bavugwa ko bamaze kwicwa
 Ibisasu vya muzinga hafi 600 nivyo bimaze guterwa muri Israel kuva ku wa gatanu, nk’uko bivugwa n’umutegetsi bwa Israel
 Israel ivuga ko ibi bitero vyaje inyuma “y’uko yari itewe” n’uyo murwi
 Iyi niyo mishamirano ikomeye hagati ya Israel na Gaza, haraciye umwaka urenga
 Intambara yamaze imisi 11  mu kwa gatanu kw’umwaka uheze wa 2021 yahitanye abanya-Palestina barenga 200 n’abanya-Israel bababa cumi imbere y’uko bashika ku masezerano yo guhagarika intambara
 Igisirikare ca Israel kiragabisha ko iki gikorwa ca gisirikare – cataziriwe Breaking Dawn – gishobora kumara iyinga ryose
 Uno musi ku wa Mungu, ibisasu vya muzinga vy’abanya-Palestina vyarasiwe mu karere ka Gaza vyaguye mu gisagara ca Jerusalem ubwa mbere kuva kuri ya ntambara yo mu 2021
 Ibi bitero  bibaye inyuma y’aho Israel yiciye umutegetsi wo ku rwego rwo hejuru wa PIJ Khaled Mansour mu gitero c’indege cakozwe ku nzu iri mw’ikambi y’impuzi iri ahitwa Rafah mu bumanuko bwa Gaza
 Iyi ntwazangabo yari imaze guhakwa kwicwa n’igisirikare ca Israel incuro zitanu, kikaba kimwagiriza gutegura ibitero vy’abarwanyi hanze y’akarere ka Gaza
 Hampande y’ibitero vy’indege kuri Gaza, aho Israel ivuga ko mu bibanza yiziziye harimwo inzira yo mu kuzimu ikoreshwa na PIJ, abahagarikwa babandanya bahagarikwa mu karere ka Cisjordanie/ West Bank kigaruriwe na Israel
 Abanywanyi ba PIJ batari bake bamaze guhagarikwa nk’uko bivugwa na Israel
 Umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu muri Gaza avuga ko "igitero ca Israel" cishe abanya-Palestina, gikomeretsa abanda barenga 200
 Israel yagiriza abarwanyi ba PIJ ko ari bo bihekuye  mu kwihenda bakica bamwe muri abo bapfuye – ikavuga ko ejo ku wa gatandatu igisasu ca muzinga ciyatse uyo muhari kikica abana batari bake i Jabalia, mu karere ka Gaza
 BBC ntiyashoboye guhinyuza yo nyene ubwayo ibi bivugwa
 Ariko gushika ubu, Hamas, umuhari mukuru muri ako karere – ukaba usangiye ivyiyumviro n’umuhari Islamic Jihad mbere ukaba ukunze gukorana ibikorwa nawo – isa n’uko ata bisasu vya muzinga biriko biraraswa biva mu bubiko bwayo bunini
 Ni naco gituma ata makuru avuga ko Israel yoba iriko irakora ibi bitero vy’indege kuri Hamas
 Mw’ijoro ryo ku wa gatanu,  Hamas yasohoye amatangazo akomeye ivuga ko “imirwi yo kwirwanako” yishize hamwe
 Ariko kubera irongoye Gaza ifise ibintu vyayo ibanza kwitondera, ibi bigashobora gutuma itinjira muri iyi mishamirano
 Ibiharuro vya Hamas bishobora guhinduka, nk’akarorero mu gihe igitigiri c’abasivire bapfiriye muri Gaza cokwongerekana
 Mu gihe yoramuka ifashe ingingo yo kwinjira muri iyi ntambara, aho rero ibintu bishobora guca bikomera gusumba
 Ejo ku wa gatandatu, ikigo ca Gaka kimwe rudende gisanzwe gitanga umuyagankuba carugaye kubera kitigeze kironka n’ima rimwe ry’igitor, nk’uko bivugwa n’umuvugizi w’ikigo kijejwe umuyagankuba
 Ibiro vy’umunyamabanga wa Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire asaba impande zompi kwifata – bikavuga ko bishigikiye ko Israel ifise uburenganzira bwo kwirwanako, mu gihe ariko bivuga ko bitewe impungenge n’abasivire bashobora kugwa mu mporero, nk’uko vyandikwa n’itirorokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters
 Mu cizere ko ishobora kuzibira iyindi mishamirano, Misiri nayo nyene yafashe umugambi wo kuja hagati y’izi mpande zibiri, mbere bikavugwa ko yoba yarungitse intumwa muri Israel ejo ku wa gatandatu kubanguranya
 Iyi mishamirano ibaye inyuma gato y’aho Israel ihagarikiye Bassem Saadi avugwa ko arongoye  PIJ muri Cisjordanie, mw’ijoro ryo ku wa mbere
 Yahagaritswe ari mu karere ka Jenin mu rukurikirane rwo guhagarika abikekwa inyuma y’ibitero vyakozwe n’abarabu ba Israel na Palestina vyahitanye abanya-Israel 17 n’abanya Ukraine babiri
 Babiri mu bakoze ivyo bitero bavuye mu karere ka Jenin
 PIJ, umwe mu mihari y’abarwanyi biyitirira Islam ikomeye irwanira muri Gaza, ishigikiwe na Irani kandi icicaro cayo kiri ku mugwa mukuru wa Syria, Damas/Damascus
 Irakora ibitero bitari bike, harimwo ibisasu vya muzinga biterwa Israel
 Mu kwa cumi na rimwe 2019, Israel na PIJ  vyaratanye mu mitwe mu kiringo c’imisi itanu inyuma y’aho Israel yiciye intwazangabo ya PIJ ivuga ko yariko arategura igitero
 Imishamirano yahitanye abanya-Palestina 34 n’abandi 111 bakomeretse, abanya-Israel 63 nabo bikaba vyabaye ngombwa ko bajanwa kwa muganga
 Israel yavuze ko 25 mu banya-Palestina bishwe bari abarwanyi, harimwo n’abatewe bariko barategura kurungika ibisasu vya muzinga

