 Ico gihe, umukuru w’umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora yaranemeye ko atari azi uwatsinze
 Aya matora ya kino gihe, nayo nyene ntibiboneka neza uwuzoyatsinda – hagati ya babiri bari imbere mu biyamamariza kurongora iki gihugu, ari bo Raila Odinga yahoze atavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi ubu ariko ariyamamaza ku ncuro ya gatanu, hamwe n’icegera c’umukuru w’igihugu William Ruto
 Mu bintu bibandanya gutangaza abantu, umukuru w’igihugu ubu arindiriye gusezera, Uhuru Kenyatta, ashigikira Odinga, umwansi yahindutse umugenzi, ko ari we yomusubirira inyuma yo gucanamwo na Ruto
 Abanyagihugu kandi bazotora ba buramatari, abashingamateka, abakenguzamateka, hamwe n’abagize amanama mpanuzwajambo
 Ariko gusa ikoreshwa ry’ubuhinga bwa none muri ano matora atatu kuva mu 2007 nta cizere riratanga  - mbere mu 2017 vyatumye Sentare nkuru y’igihugu ifuta ivyari vyatangajwe ko vyavuye mu matora haca hategurwa ayandi
 "N’aho vyagenze nabi mu 2013, haraguzwe ibikoresho vyinshi vy’ubuhinga bwa none mu 2017
 Kuri buri munyagihugu yategererwa gutora, amafaranga yakoreshejwe yavuye ku madorari y’abanyamerika 10 yo mu matora ya mbere ashika ku madorari 25 mu yakabiri, bituma Kenya imenyekana cane ko yakoze amatora azimvye muri Afrika", niko Nanjira Sambuli, umuhinga mu mu vyo intwaro n’ubuhinga bwa none  yabwiye BBC
 Uyu mukenyezi Sambuli ati: "Ubuhinga bwa none si demokarasi"
 Sentare nkuru yatangaje ko amatora yo mu kwa munani 2017 yabaye "impfagusa” mu gihe ibibanza vy’amatora vyababa 10
000 vyananiwe no gushikiriza ivyavuye mu matora
 James Mamboleo yabwiye BBC ati: "Iki cari igitigiri kinini, hanyuma umurwi ujejwe amatora utanga ivyitwazo igihe isabiwe kwugurura ububiko bw’inyabwonko kugira bihweze ivyabaye”
 "Bavuze ko umurwi ujejwe amatora ari wo ubazwa ibikorwa vyose vy’amatora, kuva ku kwandika abatora gushika batange ivyayavuyemwo”
 Iki cemezo catumye abantu batera icizere kuri Chebukati, ariko yarashoboye kubandanya n’akazi kiwe n’aho yagumye asabwa gutanga imihoho
 Ubu, umurwi ujejwe amatora uzosubira gukoresha ibikoresho ibihumbi mirongo vyo kugenzura amatora vyaguzwe mu matora ya kabiri yo mu kw’icumi 2017 kandi uyu murwi urakomeje imyiteguro
 Abantu bonyene bashobora kwemezwa n’ubu buhinga nibo bazotora kandi isanamu y’ivyayavuyemwo bizorungikwa hakoreshejwe ubu buhinga bivuye mu bibanza vy’amatora birenga 50
000 aho kurungika gusa inzandiko
 Uku niko ubu buhinga buzokoreshwa mu matora y’umukuru w’igihugu: Justus Nyangaya , umwe mu bagize umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora, yabwiye BBC ati: "Ntibizokworohera abazorondera kwitwara mu butungane muri ano matora mu ntumbero yo kwiyamiriza ibizoba biyavuyemwo kuko dukorera ku mugaragaro, ku buryo bo nyene ubwabo bazokwumva isoni zo kuja kwitwara”
 Avuga kandi ko ibikoresho vyo kugenzura abatora bizoza birarungika amakuru ku kigo c’igihugu kijejwe guharura amajwi uko amasaha abiri aheze, bikazotuma abazoba barondera kwuzuza amasandugu y’amatora n’amakarata y’ibinyoma bataronka isaganirizo
 Mu gihe akibabajwe n’amatora aheruka, umukuru w’umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora yasavye kandi ibinyamakuru, imigambwe n’amashirahamwe adaharanira ivyicaro vya poritike kwegeranya ibizoba bivuye mu matora
 Umuhinga mu vya poritike, Hesbon Owila, yabwiye BBC ati: "Chebukati yipfuza kwikosora mu gufata ingingo zose zikenewe nk’umukuru w’umurwi, anashiraho uburyo buzotuma amatora aba mu bwisanzure, mu muco, anashobore no guhinyuzwa, kugira ngo yikureko iceyi co gusiga umurage mubi nk’umukuru w’umurwi uzwi mu busuma bw’amatora
 "Nk’umuntu, ivyabaye muri kahise vyaramwigishije, gusa nk’abakenya, ico twokora ni ukumufata mu mugongo ariko kandi tukamera magabo”
 Mamboleo ati: "Ubwo umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora woba ugerageza kugendera ku mabwirizwa yashizweho n’ingingo ya Sentare nkuru y’igihugu mu 2017? Ku bwanje, ni ego
 Urakorana n’imigambwe, abahiganwa be n’abanyagihugu mu buryo tutari bwigere tubona mu matora yo muri kahise”
 Amategeko ategekanya ko umurwi ujejwe gutegura amatora ufise imisi indwi inyuma y’amatora kugira ngo utangaze uwayatsinze  - rero, mu gusaba ibinyamakuru n’abandi kwegeranya ibizoba biyavuyemwo, Chebukati afise icizere ko ugukorera mu muco kuzomweza, kukaneza n’umurwi wiwe
 Iyi izoba ari intambwe ikomeye cane kuri Kenya mu gihe ibi vyoshikwako
 Mu gihe imiryango ya Msando na Ngumbu yibuka imyaka itanu irangiye mu kwezi guheze igandaguriwe abayo, yongeye kuvuga ko demokarasi ya Kenya ari ngombwa gushimangirwa no kugendera ku mategeko - kandi yizeye ko umunsi umwe na bo bazoronswa ubutungane
 Umuryango wa Msando wanditse mu kinyamakuru kimwe muri ico gihugu uti: "Turasenga kugira ngo umunsi umwe tuzomenye ukuri"

I Goma mu buseruko bwa Republika ya demokrasi ya Congo biriwe mu muhango wo gufuba abantu cumi baguye mu myiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza ONU
 Abantu barenga 5000 nibo bitabiriye uwo muhango wo gufubira rimwe abo bantu, wabereye ku kibuga c'umupira ca Goma
 Uyu muhango ubaye nyuma y'iminsi ine habaye uwundi wo kwibuka abakozi ba ONU baguye muri iyo myiyerekano
 Imyiyerekano yadutse i Goma mu ndwi iheze kubera ishavu ry'abanyagihugu bavuga yuko abasirikare ba ONU bo mu mugwi MONUSCO bananiwe kubakingira ibitero vy'inyeshamba
 Mu muhango w'uno munsi, abarongoye amadini basavye amahoro n'ubutungane mu kwibuka abaguye mu myiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza ONU i Goma
 Bavuze yuko abapfuye bariko baraharanira amahoro, ko ku bw'ivyo rero bagomba gufatwa nk'intwari
 Benshi mu biciwe muri iyo myiyerekano bari ku kigero c'imyaka iri munsi ya 30, uwari muto muri bose akaba yari umwana w'imyaka 11
 Abitabiriye umuhango bose baguma bamanika inzandiko ziyamiriza ONU, bagasaba ko umugwi wayo uhagarariye amahoro, MONUSCO, uva mu gihugu
 MONUSCO imaze imyaka irenga cumi ikorera muri Congo, kandi ni bwo butumwa bwa ONU bwo guhagarira amahoro bufise abasikare benshi kurusha ahandi hose kw'isi
 Ariko abanyagihugu bo muri Congo bavuga yuko uwo mugwi ata mahoro na makeyi wigeze ubazanira, ko ahubwo bopfuma birwanaho bo ubwabo
 Mu ntango z'ino ndwi, icegera c'umuserukizi yihariye w'umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU muri MONUSCO, yabwiye BBC yuko ubutumwa bwa ONU bwo guhagararira amahoro buzotahukanwa
 Yongerako yuko hazoshirwako umugambi witondewe wo kubusubira buke buke mu buseruko bwa Congo

Umukuru w'ishami rya Onu rigenzura inguvu za nucléaire, avuga ko uruganda runini rw'inguvu za nucléaire  rwigaruriwe n'Uburusiya inyuma y'ibitero bwagize muri Ukraine, " ata n'umwe arwitayeho"
 Rafael Grossi yasubiwemwo n'itororokanirizo ry'amakuru rya Associated Press avuga ko uruganda rwa Zaporizhzhia rukeneye kugenzurwa no gukorwa
 Yavuze ati:"Ufise urutonde rw'ibintu bitategerezwa na rimwe gushika ku ruganda urwo ari rwo rwose rw'ubumara
" Urwo ruganda rwa mbere runini rw'inguvu za nucléaire i Buraya rwegereye biteye ubwoba ahabera imigwano
 Mu ntango y'iyi ndwi, umunyamabanga wa reta wa Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire Antony Blinken yagirije Uburusiya  gukoresha urwo ruganda, bwigaruriye mu kwezi kwa batatu, nk'ikirindiro ca gisirikare bukoresha mu kugira ibitero ku ngabo za Ukraine
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine bavuze ko abarusiya bashize ingabo n'ibikoresho vya gisirikare kuri urwo ruganda ruri ku ruzi Dnipro mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Ariko umutegetsi yashizweho n'Uburusiya muri ako karere yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru rya Reuters ko abasirikare ba Ukraine bakoresha ibigwanisho bahawe n'abanye Buraya mu kugira ibitero kuri urwo ruganda
 Yevgeny Balitsky yavuze ko abategetsi biteguye kwereka urwego Grossi arongoye rugenzura inguvu za nucleaire kw'isi (IAEA), uko abarusiya bacungereye urwo ruganda mu gihe abanye Ukraine bagirizwa kurugirako ibitero
 Igihe Uburusiya bwafata urwo ruganda, iterwa ry'ibimbombe kuri izo nyubakwa  ryatumye haba ukunebagurwa kw'isi yose
 Urwo ruganda ruracakora, abakoze b'abanye Ukraine bari ku kazi ariko bagenzurwa n'Uburusiya
 Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ku cicaro ca Onu i New York, Grossi yagize ati:"Ibintu vyifashe nabi cane
 Ingingo iyo ari yo yose yerekeye gukingira uruganda rwa nucleaire yarahonyanzwe mu nzira iyi canke iriya, ntidushobora kwemera ko ivyo bibandanya
" Uwo muyobozi wa IAEA avuga ko ariko aragerageza kwegeranya abantu bogira urugendo vuba hashoboka kuri urwo ruganda ariko ko ivyo bikeneye uruhusha rw'impande zose, Ukraine n'Uburusiya, hamwe na Onu, ufatiye ku ngorane zo kugendera akarere kaberamwo intambara

Umushingamateka Agathon Rwasa arongoye umugambwe CNL abona ko amajambo aherutse gushikirizwa n'umukuru w'igihugu yiyamiriza indongozi n’abajejwe umutekano bagira uruhara mu bwicanyi ari “ugusigana inkore ku maso kuko ubwicanyi bukorwa n’abantu bitwa y’uko bari mu nzego bwaramaze kuba nk’akamenyero”
 Ku wa gatatu w’indwi iheze, igihe yariko atanga inyigisho zo gukunda no gukundisha igihugu ku Barundi baba mu mahanga, Perezida Evariste Ndayishimiye yavuze ko ababazwa n’indongozi irera amaboko abantu bariko baricwa
 Ndayishimiye yaremeje ko hari n’akarwi k’abicanyi kakoresha abajejwe umutekano bikitirirwa reta
 Kubw’umushingamateka Rwasa, abantu, mbere n’abanywanyi biwe, bamye bicwa izuba riva, ubutungane ntihagire ico bukora
 Yabwiye BBC ati: “Rero kuvuga ngo uno musi biramutangaza


sinzi y’uko wewe ivyo vyaba vyose atabibona canke atavyumva
 “Kuri twebwe amajambo biraryoshe kuyumva, mugabo iciza ni uko twari kubona afata ingingo zituma koko bihagarara”
 Mw’itangazo ryasohoye mu kwa kabiri 2022, Ligue Iteka, rimwe mu mashirahamwe yafuswe mu Burundi, yavuze ko kuva Perezida Ndayishimiye ashitse ku butegesi hari hamaze kwicwa abantu 1241
 Ligue Iteka ivuga ko muri icyo kiringo nyene hatorwa ibiziga 430, 104 baburwa irengero
 Iri shirahamwe ryagirije umuhari w’urwaruka rw’umugambwe uri ku butegetsi, IMBONERAKURE,  ko  ari wo ahanini ukora ayo mabi, ibirego uyu muhari na reta y’Uburundi bamye yiyamiriza
 Muri izo nyigisho, Ndayishimiye yavuze ko ibihe igihugu caciyemwo bibabaje cane, ko no mu misi iheze hari akarwi kari kagisibije, mbere kanakoresha abajejwe umutekano, bikitirirwa reta
 Ati: “Mu misi iheze kugira ngo dutore akarwi kakidnapa (kanyuruza) abantu, urazi ingene vyaturuhishije? “Bavuga ngo ni reta, ngo reta iriko irica abantu, bakandika mu  ma medias yose ko reta iriko irica abantu, kandi hariho akarwi kariko karica abantu! “Nagiye kwemera neza nsanze ako karwi gakoresha n’abajejwe umutekano”
 Asaba abanyagihugu kugira urunani bakiruka ku bicanyi gushika babafashe
 Ati: “Tudafatanye mu nda - ni ukuvuga tubonye umurundi ahuye n’ivyago, tukarondera uwateye ivyo vyago kugira tumufate twese - tuzokwama dufise abicanyi”
 Mu matora y’umukuru w’igihugu yabaye mu 2020, Evariste Ndayishimiye niwe yayatsinze ku majwi 68%, Agathon Rwasa aza ubwa kabiri n'amajwi 24%
 Abajijwe nimba yemera ko aka karwi k’abicanyi kavugwa na Ndayishimiye karatujijwe, umushingamateka Rwasa abona ko atari vyo kandi ko kabandanya kiha inkumbi
 Ati: “Rero hariho imvugo novuga ko ari iyo kuryohera amatwi y’abarundi tugire ngo turitaweho, mugabo ukuri kuriho ni uko inyungu z’abanyagihugu sizo ziraje ishinga muvyo ukuri
 “Nimba baragatujije, none abo twumva ngo batorwa ibiziga hirya no hino, vyoba bikorwa na bande”? “Ibikorwa bibi birabandanya kuko hari igihe wumva ngo aha kanaka bahasanze ikiziga, bagaca bamuhamba ata matohoza abaye, ivyo ni ibintu vyama vyabaye”
 Nayo ku kamo atera abanyagihugu ngo bafatane mu nda barwanye ako karwi, Rwasa abona ko vyari vyiza, ariko ko bidashoboka “mu gihe reta, inzego z’igihugu ataco ziriko zirakora ngo zifashe abo banyagihugu”
 Ati: “Ugira gutya ukumva ngo abantu banyurujwe hirya no hino, ubutungane ntihagire ico bukora, inzego zijejwe amatohoza mu gipolisi ntihagire ico zikora kugira ngo tumenye abo bantu bapfuye ni ba nde, bishwe bigenze gute
 “None abanyagihugu, gufatana mu nda kwabo kwogenda gute mu gihe inzego zijejwe guhana inkozi z’ibibi ataco ziriko zirafasha? “Iyo abantu babonye hatowe ikiziga ahantu, uwo muntu agahamba ata matohoza akozwe, none wumva uyo muntu nyarucari nawe azoshobora gufasha iki”? Atanga akarorero k’umuntu wo mu ntara ya Gitega avuga ko yishe umuntu, mu gatondo bakamufatana itonga ariko arayererana ikiziga arondera aho agihamba
 Ati: “Uyo muntu baramushize muri sentare ariko amatwi adusumira, ubu yoba yidegemvya
 “None iyo umuntu yishe umuntu, akamara mu munyororo umwanya urume rumara, mugabo uwivye igitoke canke uwadenderejwe akamarayo imyaka mirongo canke ubuzima bwiwe bwose, abo banyagihugu bazofatana mu nda ngo batuze ububisha nka bene ubwo gute kandi ushobora gusanga abakora mwene ivyo bintu boba bafise ababa babashigikiye, n’iyo bafashwe baca babarekura muri ubwo buryo?”
