 Ariko igihe BBC yagendera akarere ka Nyeri - kari mu ntara ya Mount Kenya igwiriyemwo abakikuyu - vyaragaragaye ko urukundo bari bamufitiye rwagabanutse kubera ingingo yafashe yo gushigikira Odinga  muco yise kwunga ubumwe inyuma y'imyaka itari mike y'imishamirano
 Umunyamategeko Wahome Gikonyo we yumva ko Kenyatta yahemukiye Ruto, yamufashije gutsinda mu matora incuro zibiri zose  bahanganye na Odinga
 Avugana na BBC mu biro vyiwe biri mu gisagara kinini co muri iyo ntara, Nyeri, Gikonyo yagize ati: "Ruto yakoze akazi k'indogobwe mu 2013 na 2017
 Iyo ataba we, Uhuru ntiyari kuba prezida
 Uko ni ko umuntu asubiriza mu ndumane umugenzi?" Bamwe mu bahaba nk'umukozi w'Imana Hannah Kanyuthere, yumva ko Kenyatta atari akwiye kuja mu ntambara yo kurondera uwuzomusubirira
 Yongeyeko ati: "Kubera iki prezida yagize uruhande yegamiye muri aya matora? N'aho icegera ciwe coba kibi gute, yategerezwa kutagira uruhande yegamiye
" Ariko umudereva wa Taxi, Hassan Kahoro  we arashigikiye Kenyatta, avuga ko, kubera ikibazo c'amoko ari co kiza imbere muri politike ya Kenya, igihe cari kigeze kugira abo mu bwoko bw'aba Luo na bo baronke umuprezida - Odinga
 Igihe yariko arashikiriza ijambo abantu bari bakoraniye kw'isoko nkuru, Kahoro yagize ati: "Dutegerezwa guha akaryo aba Luo na bo batware
 Ninde yavuze ko igihugu gitegerezwa gutwarwa n'abakikuyu gusa hamwe n'abakalenjine?" Aha yashaka kuvuga ko mu baprezida bane bamaze gutwara Kenya kuva yikukiye, batatu ari abakikuyu
 Umuhisi Daniel arap Moi - yatwaye umwanya muremure, imyaka 24 - akaba yari umukalenjine, ubwoko basangiye na Ruto
 Na Welder Jackson Maina na we nyene ashigikiye ingingo ya Kenyatta yo gushigikira "Baba", canke "Data" izina abayoboke ba Raila w'imyaka 77 bamutaziriye
 Ahagaze hanze y'aho adandariza, yagize ati: "Turashigikiye twivuye inyuma prezida rero turi inyuma ya Baba
" Igisagara ca Nyeri cuzuyemwo ibitambara n'ibindi bakoresha mu kwiyamamaza mu gihe amatora yegereje
 Indirimbo zihayagiza abitoza bose zirumvikana hose
 Indirimbo imwe - y'umuririmvyi rurangiranwa muri Kenya Ben Githae - ivuga ko Kenya izoba ari nyabagendwa irongowe na Odinga bari kumwe na Martha Karua - yahoze ari umushikiranganji w'ubutungane akaba n'umukikuyu "umukobwa w'imvukira" ya Mount Kenya
 Urundi ruririmbo - rw'umunyepolitike Betty Maina - ruhamagarira abantu gusidukana n'iyonka gutora Ruto, yahisemwo umukikuyu w'umugwizatunga wo mu karere ka Nyeri ngo azomubere icegera, Rigathi Gachagua
 N'aho Gachagua afise ikibazo co kuguma yagirizwa igiturire, n'umuntu azi kwegeranya abantu benshi mu myiyamamazo kandi yumvirwa n'abakikuyu bafise ubuzima bubayabaye
 Umupfasoni Karua ni rurangiranwa n'ahandi atari mu bakikuyu gusa - akaba azwi cane mu mwete wiwe wo gusubiramwo ivyerekeye ubutungane no kugwanya igiturire muri reta
 Ariko mu gihe umuntu yofatira ku biharuro biherutse kwerekanwa na Tifa, yaba we cane Kenyatta, nta n'umwe yashoboye kugondoza abakikuyu benshi gutora Odinga
 Ivyo biharuro vyerekana ko Ruto ari we aza imbere mu biharuro muri Mount Kenya - ku majwi 66% mu gihe Odinga ari 27%
 Ku rwego rw'igihugu, uko ibintu vyifashe biratandukanye, aho ibiharuro bishira imbere Odinga n'amajwi 46
7% - amajwi atamuha intsinzi yo kuba prezida, kuko kugira atahukane intsinzi ategerezwa kuronka amajwi 50% kugira ntihabe amatora agira kabiri
 Impande ko ari zibiri rero zitegerezwa gukoresha inguvu nyinshi mu kugondoza abazoja mu matora kubaha amajwi mu misi ya nyuma yo kwiyamamaza
 Ingingo ya Kenyatta yo gushigikira Odinga ntiyacanishijemwo gusa abakikuyu - bagize igice kinini c'abatora - n'umuryango wiwe n'uko
 Muvyarawe Kungu Muigai yabwiye ibinyamakuru vyo muri Kenya ko prezida atisunze ingingo y'abakurambere b'abakikuyu mu gusuzugura umwumvikano wo mu 2013, wasaba ko mu kwishura boshigikira abakalenjine igihe ibiringo bibiri vyiwe bizoba biheze
 Uko gucanamwo kuranebagurwa n'abakurambere b'abakikuyu, nka Nduhiu Njama w'imyaka 100, yatwakiriye ku muhana iwe i Tetu mu karere ka Nyeri
 Atwereka ifoto zo muri kahise yagize ati: "Twaronse intahe yo kwikukira kubera twari dufatanye mu nda
 Ubu ivyo tubona ni ukwigungirako kuzodukorako
" Abakikuyu benshi n'abarimyi
 Imirima y'ikawa n'icayi hamwe n'impongore z'inka zikamwa ni vyo bikwiragiye mu karere ka Mount Kenya
 Amabaraba mu misozi akozwe neza ku buryo vyorohera abarimyi gutwara ivyo bimbuye
 BBC yaragendeye abarimyi hagufi y'igisagara ca Othaya, ahahoze haba umuhisi prezida Mwai Kibaki
 Mu gihe yariko aragaburira inka ziwe zikamwa yavuze ko ashigikiye Ruto
 Uwo mugabo w'imyaka 40, afise abana batatu, avuga ico yiyumvira ku matora basangiye n'abandi benshi yagize ati: "Ruto n'umurimyi nkanje kandi igihe yari umushikiranganji w'uburimyi yarazanye impinduka zatumye abarimyi b'icayi baronka agasunuzo kanini katari bwaboneke
 Ndazi ko azoteza imbere igisata c'uburimyi
" Ariko bamwe baranse kugira ico bavuga k'uwo bashigikiye - bikaba bidatangaje mu gihe impari zisa nizikomeye
 Ariko yamura ikawa yiwe iteye muri hegitari 80, Mercy Muthoni, afise abana bane yagize ati: "Twikenereye imfashanyo y'umwavu reta yoduha kugira umwimbu w'ikawa yacu wongerekane
" Aho ni mu gihe uwurongoye ishirahamwe ry'abarimyi b'i Othaya, Gathua Nderitu we avuga ko ata n'umwe ashigikiye muri aya matora
 Yabwiye BBC ati: "Nta co mu vy'ukuri nitayeho ku wuzoba prezida inyuma y'itariki 9 z'ukwezi kw'umunani
"
Umutegetsi wo ku rwego rwo hejuru mu mugambwe w'aba-Democrats uri ku butegetsi muri Amerika, Nancy Pelosi, ari muri Taiwan mu muce w'urugendo arimwo muri Aziya, naho Ubushinwa bwari bwagabishije
 Uru rugendo, rudashigikiwe na Prezida Biden, ni rwo rwambere rugizwe muri Taiwan n'umutegetsi akomeye wa Amerika mu kiringo c'imyaka mirongo
 Ubushinwa bubona Taiwan, isa n'iyigenga, nk'intara yayo yiyonkoye ariko bitebe bitebuke ikaba izosubira kuba igice c'igihugu
 Uburusiya n'Ubushinwa vyari vyagabishije Amerika yuko urugendo rwa Pelosi ari agasombororotsi kandi ko ruhungabanya
 Maison Blanche/White House (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu wa Amerika) iragabisha ko Ubushinwa bushobora gusotora bukoresheje uburyo bwa gisirikare mu kwihora urugendo ruteje impari rwa Nancy Pelosi  muri Taiwan
 Muri aka gasotoro harimwo gutera ibisasu vya misire hafi ya Taiwan, canke ibikorwa vya gisirikare bikomeye mu kirere canke mu mazi, nk’uko umuvugizi wa Maison Blanche John Kirby abivuga
 Ibinyamakuru vya Taiwan na Amerika bivuga ko ategekanya kugendera Taipei (umugwa mukuru wa Taiwan), ariko ntibiremezwa na reta ya Amerika
 Pékin/Beijing (umugwa mukuru w’Ubushinwa) igabisha ko hazoba “inkurikizi zikomeye” mu gihe Pelosi yoramuka agiyeyo
 Mu gihe Amerika ibandanya ico yita “imigenderanire ikomeye ariko itazwi” na Taiwan, ifitaniye imigenderanire n’Ubushinwa izwi, ariko atari Taiwan
 Ku wa mbere, umuserukizi w’Ubushinwa muri ONU Zhang Jun yaragabishije ko uru rugendo rushobora guhungabanya imigenderanire hagati ya Pékin na Washington, nk’uko itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters rivyandika
 Impande zompi mu migambwe ibiri irwanira ubutegetsi muri Amerika zirashigikiye cane Taiwan, co kimwe no mu nama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka
 Ni mu gihe Pelosi, umutegetsi mukuru mu mugambwe w’aba Democrats, kuva kera yamye anegura ubutegetsi bw’Ubushinwa, yiyamiriza ihonyanga ry’agateka ka zina muntu ryo ku rwego rwo hejuru
 Yarigeze kubonana n’abarwanira intwaro rusangi mbere aragendera ikibanza ciswe Tiananmen Square i Pékin mu kwibuka abaguye mu bwicanyi bwo mu 1989
 Uyu mukuru w’inama nshingamateka yatanguye urugendo rwiwe muri Aziya ku wa Mungu, bikaba bitegekanijwe ko aca muri Singapour, Malaysia, Korea y’Epfo no mu Buyapani
 Yategekanya kugendera Taiwan mu kwa kane, ariko yarungurije urugendo rwiwe inyuma y’aho yanduriye Covid-19
 Mu ntango za kuno kwezi, Pelosi yavuze ko vyari “nkenerwa kuri twebwe kwereka Taiwan ko tuyishigikiye”
 Perezida Joe Biden avuga ko igisirikare ca Amerika cemera ko urugendo rwa Pelosi muri Taiwan atari “iciyumviro ciza muri kino gihe”
 Ku wa mbere, umuvugizi wa Maison Blanche mu gisata c’umutekano w’igihugu John Kirby yavuze ko mu vyo Ubushinwa bushobora gukora mu kwunyura ibintu ari “ugushinga imanza z’amanyanga” mu misi iri imbere, nk’akarorero bukavuga ko Umuhora wa Taiwan (Détroit de Taïwan / Taiwan Strait ) atari umugezi mpuzamakungu
 Avuga ko ibindi bimenyetso vyerekana ko Pékin ishobora kurungika indege z’itambara muri iryo zinga, nka kimwe mu bigize ibikorwa vyo kuvogera ikirere ca Taiwan
 Kirby asigura ko uwahoze ari umukuru w’inama nshingamateka w’Umurepubulika Newt Gingrich yigeze kugendera Taiwan mu 1997, kandi ko n’abandi bashingamateka ba Amerika bagendeye Taiwan mu ntango z’uno mwaka
 Avuga ati: "Nta cahindutse
 Ntaco twovuga kidasanzwe
 Si bwo bwa mbere umukuru w’inama nshingamateka azoba agendeye Taiwan”
 Yongerako y’uko Pelosi arerurwa n’indege za Amerika muri uru rugendo rwo muri Aziya
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije muri ONU, umunyamabanga wa Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire Antony Blinken asaba Ubushinwa kwinengesera mu gihe Pelosi yogendera Taiwan
 Inyuma y’ibiganiro vyo kurwanya ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri i New York, Blinken yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Mu gihe umukuru w’inama nshingamateka yofata ingingo yo gukora uru rugendo, hanyuma Ubushinwa bukagerageza guteza ingorane canke naho bugatuma ibintu vyunyuka, vyose bizoba biri ku gatwe ka Pékin”
 "Turiteze ko – mu gihe yoramuka afashe ingingo yo kugendera Taiwan – ivyo bokora vyose bokwinengesera hagukora ikintu ico ari co cose cotuma ibintu vyunyuka”

Ingabo z’aba Taliban bari ku butegetsi muri Afghanistan zatanye mu mitwe n’ingabo za Iran izijejwe gucungera imipaka ku rubibe ibi bihugu bihana
 Aba Taliban bavuga ko umwe mu basirikare babo yishwe muri ino ngwano y’ejo ku wa Mungu, yabereye mu karere kari hagati y’intara ya Nimroz ya Afghanistan n’akarere ka Hirmand ka Iran
 Kimwe cose cagiriza ikindi ko ari co casotoye
 Kuva abarwanyi b’aba Taliban bigaruriye ubutegetsi muri Afghanistan, haraciye umwaka, hama haba ukurasana ku rubibe ibi bihugu bihana
 Icateye iyi mishamirano y’ubu ntikiramenyekana
 Bahram Haqmal , umuvugizi w’igipolisi mu ntara ya Nimroz, yabwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters ati: "Dufise umwe yishwe n’uwundi yakomeretse”
 Mu ntara ya Sistan va Baluchestan ya Irani, umutegetsi wa Hirmand, Maysam Barazandeh, yasubiwemwo n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Fars ryo muri Irani avuga ko ku ruhande rwa Irani ata n’umwe yapfuye canke ngo akomereke
 Itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Tasnim ryo muri Irani ritangaza ko iyi ngwano yadutse igihe ingabo z’aba Taliban zigeragereje kuduza ibendera ryabo “mu karere kategukira Afghanistan”, haca haduka ukurasana kwamaze “iminota itari mike”
 Barazandeh  ati: "Ingabo zacu zarishuye uko vyari bikenewe”
 Mu kwezi guheze, umushikiranganji wa Irani ajejwe imigenderanire yatangaje ko hari umwe mu ngabo zayo zijejwe gucungera imbibe yishwe mu mishamirano yabereye muri ako karere nyene

