Ubwato bwa mbere butwaye intete bwahagurutse ku kivuko ca Ukraine hisunzwe amasezerano y'akataraboneka n'Uburusiya
 Abategetsi ba Turkia na Ukraine bavuze ko ubwo bwato bwavuye ku kivuko co mu bumanuko ca Odesa kare mu gitondo ku musi wa mbere
 Kuva mu kwezi kwa kabiri, Uburusiya bwari bwugarije ico kivuko ca Ukraine, ariko izo mpande zibiri zarumvikanye ku masezerano yo kureka ubwato butwaye intete bukarengana
 Vyitezwe ko ayo masezerano azotuma ibifungurwa bisubira kuboneka kw'isi, anagabanure igiciro c'intete
 Turkia yavuze ko ubwo bwato buriko idarapo rya Sierra Leone, bwitwa Razoni, bushobora gushikira ku kivuko ca Tripoli muri Libani, yongerako ko hari n'ubundi bwato butegekanijwe guhaguruka mu ndwi ziri imbere
 Ikigo co kugenzura ico gikorwa gihuriyemwo n'impande zose, cashinzwe hisunzwe ayo masezerano i Istanbul, cavuze ko ubwo bwato butwaye amatoni 26
000 y'ibigori, bikaba vyitezwe ko bushika mu mazi ya Turkia kugira bugenzurwe ku musi wa kabiri
 Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Onu Antonio Guterres yakiranye urweze iryo haguruka ry'ubwo bwato anashimagiza Turkia ku ruhara yagize mw'ishirwa mu bikorwa ry'ayo masezerano
 Umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe inyubako, Alexander Kubrakov yanditse kuri Facebook ati: "Uyu musi Ukraine, turi kumwe n'abo dukorana, twagize iyindi ntambwe mu gukinga inzara kw'isi
" "Iyugururwa ry'ibivuko rizotuma haboneka imiriyaridi imwe avuye mu guhanahana ibidandazwa hamwe n'akaryo keza ku gisata c'uburimyi ko kwitegurira umwaka uza
" Mu gihe ubwo bwato bwera bwa Ruzoni bugaragara mu mazi y'ikiyaga cirabura cuzuyemwo amamine vyerekana intambwe ishimishije, ico gikorwa gitegerezwa kumara igihe kirekire kugira kigirire akamaro ubutunzi bwa Ukraine bubangamiwe cane no kugira abantu ama miliyoni bageramiwe n'inzara kw'isi bacungukiremwo
 Ariko Kubrakov yavuze ko ayandi mato 16 arindiriye guhaguruka ku bivuko vyo mu karere ka Odesa mu ndwi ziri imbere
 Amasezerano yo mu kwezi guheze - yahagarikiwe na Onu hamwe na Turkia - yafashe amezi abiri kugira ashikweko bikaba bitegekanijwe ko amara imisi 120
 Ashobora kwongererezwa ikiringo mu gihe impande zose zobihurizako

Habaye imyiyerekano i Beni mu buseruko bwa Republika ya Demokrasi ya Congo yo kwiyamiriza ibikorwa vy'abasirikare ba ONU bahagarariye amahoro muri ako karere
 Abantu baharurirwa mu mirongo bihaye amabarabara nyuma y'umunsi umwe abasirikare ba ONU barashe abantu babiri bakabica bagakomeretsa n'abandi cumi na batanu
 Ivyo vyabereye ku rubibe igihugu ca Congo gihana n'ica Uganda, ONU ikavuga yuko ubu abo basirikare bafashwe
 Hagati aho habaye umuhango wo kwunamira abasirikare batatu ba ONU bari mu bantu mirongo ibiri bishwe mu ndwi iheze mu myiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza ukuba kw'abasirikare ba ONU mu buseruko bw'igihugu
 Abanye-Congo benshi bavuga yuko abo basirikare bananiwe gukingira abanyagihugu ibitero vyinshi vy'inyeshamba
 Uwujejwe ibikorwa vyo guhagararira amahoro muri ONU yavuze yuko impfu z'abasirikare benshi ba ONU ziheruka zongereje ingongo z'igikorwa co kugarukana amahoro muri Congo

Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko igisirikare c’Uburusiya kiriko kirakomeza ibirindiro vyaco mu turere cigaruriye mu bumanuko bw’igihugu, ariko ko ata mahirwe bufise yo gutsinda iyi ntambara
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe rya nijoro ku wa Mungu, Zelenksy yavuze ati: "Nashaka gushimira abanyagihugu bose ba Nikolaev ku kungene batemera guhonyorwa ku gakanu, ku kungene barwanira igisagara n’intara yabo
 “Ndashimira kandi Nikopol, Kharkov, Krivoy Rog hamwe n’intara yose ya Dnepropetrovsk, intara ya Zaporozhye n’abanyagihugu bayo bihagararako, abanya-Ukraine bose bo mu ntara ya Kherson, umuntu wese yitanga mu gukingira Odessa
 “Ndabashimiye ku butwari bwanyu! Uburusiya nta mahirwe yo gutsinda intambara”
 Hagati aho, ingabo z'Uburusiya muri iri joro ryakeye zacucagiye amabombe mu gisagara ca Nikolaev, nk’uko bivugwa n’umukuru w’iki gisagara, Alexander Senkevich
 Yanditse ku rubuga rwa Telegram  ati: "Nikolaev irasubiriye guterwa
 Ibibombe bikomeye biriko biracucagirwa mu turere dutandukanye tw’igisagara
 Turiko turegeranya amakuru
 Mwigire kure y’amadirisha kandi ntimwibagire amabwirizwa yo kwikingira”
 Ni mu gihe ikigo ca Amerika cigisha ivy’intambara (Institute for the Study of War, ISW) kivuga ko ingabo z’’Uburusiya ziriko zirategura akarere mu ntumbero yo gutera Kharkov
 Abahinga b’iki kigo mu cegeranyo cabo gishasha, bandika ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zasubiriye gukora ibitero vyo ku butaka mu buraruko bushira uburengero no mu bumanuko bushira uburengero bwa Izyum kandi ko bashobora kuba bariko barategura ibindi bitero mu burengero bwa Kharkiv canke amaja muri Kharkov
 Aba bahinga kandi bandika bati: "Haraciye amezi atari make ingabo z’Uburusiya zishinze ibirindiro mu micungararo ya Balakliya na Velikaya Kamyshevakha, zikaba zishobora gukoresha utu turere tubiri mu gutegura igitero”
 Kubw’aba bahinga, ingabo z’Uburusiya nta mahirwe zifise yo kwigarurira intara ya Kharkiv canke kwigarurira igisagara ca Kharkiv – igisagara kigira kabiri gifise abantu benshi muri Ukraine – uravye ingene intambara ya Donbas igenda bukebuke n’ingorane zibandanya zijanye n’ingabo n’uburyo
 Aba bahinga bavuga kandi ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zishobora gukora ibitero vyo gutesha ivy’ingabo za Ukraine zirondera kwisubiza uturere zatakaje
 Ni mu gihe igisata kijejwe igendereza c’Ubwongereza kivuba ko Uburusiya bushobora gusubiramwo integuro y’intambara yabwo mu karere ka Donbas
 Kivuga ko inyuma y’aho bunaniriwe gushika ku ntumbero yabwo zari zifitiye Donbas kuva mu kwa kane, Uburusiya bushobora kuba bwaramaze kubona akandi karere, Zaporozhye, zishobora kwizizira
 Iki gisata kimenyesha ko mu misi ine iheze, Uburusiya bwabandanije ibitero mu karere ka  Bakhmut kari mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw’intara ya Donetsk, ariko ko umuvuduko wari muto
 Gisubiramwo kandi ivyashikirijwe n’abategetsi ba Ukraine mu ndwi iheze ko Uburusiya bushobora kuba buriko burimurira mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine

