 "Hariho nk'uwitwa Janvier Nkurunziza, hariho uwitwa Olivier Buyoya, hariho Fred Ngoga, bafata bakandika neza bakangirira note nk'uko boba ari aba 'conseillers' (abahanuzi) turi kumwe ngaha
