Ku wa gatatu, ababetetsi ba Irani baranyonze abagore batatu bagiriwe n’icaha co kwica abagabo babo, nk’uko bivugwa n’ishirahamwe riharanira agateka ka muntu muri ico gihugu
 Iryo shirahamwe, Iran Human Rights Group, rivuga ko abo bari mu bantu 32 banyonzwe mu kiringo c’indwi imwe gusa
 Umugore yarongowe akiri umwana, yagiye kwagirwa n’icaha c’uko yahavuye yica umugabo yari yamurongoye afise imyaka 15, ni umwe muri bo
 Abategetsi ba Irani bazwi ko bongereje akariro mu gucira abantu imanza zo gupfa, aho bamaze kunyonga abantu bangana incuro zibiri gushika ubu ugereranije n’umwaka uheze
 Amashirahamwe aharanira agateka ka zina muntu avuga ko Iran kandi ari co gihugu ca mbere kinyonga abagore, abenshi muri bo bakavugwa ko bagirwa n’icaha co kugandagura abagabo babo
 Ku wa gatatu, ishirahamwe Iran Human Rights Group ryavuze ko uyu mugore Soheila Abadi yari yarongowe akiri umwana, yanyongewe mw’ibohero amaze kwagirwa n’icaha co kwica umugabo wiwe yari yamurongoye afise imyaka 15 bakaba bari bamaranye imyaka cumi
 Sentare yaciye uru rubanza ivuga ko “indyane zo mu muryango” ari zo zatumye uyu mugore yica umugabo wiwe
 Abandi bagore babiri banyonzwe ku wa gatatu nabo nyene bagiriwe n’icaha co kwica abagabo babo, nk’uko iri shirahamwe ribivuga
 Abaharanira agateka ka zina muntu bavuga ko nyinshi muri izi manza ziba zirimwo ihohotera rikorerwa mu ngo, ariko ko amasentare ya Irani adakunze kubifatirako
 Ibiharuro nyavyo vy’abanyongwa ntibizwi kuko abategetsi ba Irani badatangaza ku mugaragaro buri muntu anyonzwe
 Icigwa cakozwe mu kwa kane n’amashirahamwe abiri aharanira agateka ka muntu, cerekana ko ibice 16
5% vy’abazwi ko banyonzwe mu mwaka uheze ari bo batangajwe
 Ivyegeranyo vyerekana ko igihano c’urupfu ciyongereye
 Amnesty International muri ino ndwi yagirije Irani ko, kuva mu mezi aheze, yafashe ingendo “iteye ubwoba” yo kunyonga, aho abantu barenga 250 aribo banyonzwe mu mezi atandatu ya mbere y’uno mwaka wa 2022
 Abo ni incuro zirenga zibiri ku gitigiri c’abanyonzwe mu mwaka uheze mu kiringo nk’iki
 Icegera c’umukuru w'akarere muri Amnesty International, Diana Eltahawy avuga ati: "Reta iriko irica ku bwinshi mu gihugu cose, mu gitero giteye ubwoba kibangamiye uburenganzira bwo kubaho
" Iri shirahamwe rivuga ko bamwe mu bagirwa n’icaha banyongwa ikivunga, harimwo n’abaharurwa mw’icumi banyongewe mw’ibohero rimwe ku wa 15 Ruheshi (6),  igitigiri nk’ico nyene mu rindi bohero ku wa 6 Ruheshi
 Inkehwa kandi nizo nyinshi muri ibi biharuro
 N’aho bangana hafi 5% y’abanyagihugu bose ba Iran, abanyagihugu bo mu bwoko bw’inkwehwa bw’aba Baluchi barenga ica kane muri abo Amnesty International izi ko bamaze kunyongwa gushika ubu uno mwaka

Mu gihe Uburusiya bwaciwe n’ibihugu vy’Uburengero kubera intambara yabwo muri Ukraine,   umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire wabwo, Sergei Lavrov, yasasiwe indava mu rugendo rwiwe yakoze mu bihugu bine vya Afrika
 Urugendo rwa Lavrov rwerekanye ko Uburusiya bugifise inguvu mu bijanye n’imigenderanire ku buryo bushobora guhangana n’Uburengero mu kwigarurira imitima y’abategetsi ba Afrika, ni mu gihe yari mu rugendo mu Misiri, muri Ethiopia, Uganda na Congo-Brazzaville
 Ibihugu hafi vyose vya Afrika – harimwo Nigeria na Kenya, ibihugu bitunze vya Afrika y’Uburengero na Afrika y’Ubuseruko uko bikurikirana – vyaratoye icemezo c’shirahamwe ONU ciyamiriza igitero c’Uburusiya mu kwa gatatu, kinasaba Uburusiya kuva muri Ukraine
 Hagati aho, hafi igice c’ibihugu biterekanye aho vyegamiye – 17 – ni ivya Afrika
 Muri ibi harimwo Afrika y’Epfo – ibona ko ifitiye ideni Moscou kubera yayishigikiye muri rwa rugamba rwo kurwanya intwaro y’abazungu  bari inkehwa – hamwe na Uganda, igihugu citeze kurongora umuhari w’ibihugu ataho vyegamiye (Mouvement des Non-Alignes/ Non-Aligned Movement ), ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryashinzwe muri ca gihe c’intambara yo kwikekana  (Guerre Froide/Cold War) n’ibihugu bitashaka kwisanga mu ndyane zari hagati y’ibihugu vy’Uburengero n’ibihugu vya gikomunista
 Mu kiganiro n’abamenyeshamakuru ari kumwe na Lavrov, Perezida Yoweri Museveni  wa Uganda yashimangiye ingingo yiwe yo kutagira aho yegamiye mu ntambara ya Ukraine
 Ati: "Ntabwo twemera kuba abansi b’umwansi w’umuntu”
 Kuri Lavrov, uru rugendo rwari nkenerwa mu kurwanya amajambo avugwa ko Uburusiya buriko “burateza intambara” muri Afrika
 Ariyamiriza ibihano Uburusiya bwafatiwe n’ibihugu vy’Uburengero vyatumye ibiciro vy’intete biba umurengera
 Nta mfashanyo yemereye ibihugu vya Afrika mu gutorera inyishu ingaruka z’ikibazo c’ubuzima buzimvye
 Ibi  bitandukanye n’ibiherutse gushikirizwa na Amerika, aho yemerera ibihugu vya Afrika imiriyaridi 1
3 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika mu ntumbero yo kurwanya inzara, canke n’akigoro k’Ubufaransa gaciye mw’ishirahamwe Food and Agriculture Resilience Mission (FARM) mu ntumbero yo gufasha  igisata c’uburimyi muri Afrika
 Perezida Emmanuel Macron  w’Ubufaransa nawe muri ino ndwi ari mu rugendo muri Afrika, aho agendera Cameroun, Benin na Guinea-Bissau
 Muri Cameroun yavuze ati: "Turagirizwa na bamwe bamwe bavuga ko ibihano vyafashwe n’Ubulaya ari vyo vyateje ikibazo c’imfungurwa kw’isi, harimwo na Afrika
 Ibi si vyo na gato
 Imfungurwa, co kimwe n’ibitoro, vyabaye ikirwanisho c’Uburusiya”
 Mu kubeshuza ibi, Lavrov yavuze ko ikibazo c’imfungurwa catanguye mu gihe ca Covid, ariko akaba yaremeye ko “ingorane ya Ukraine yongereje ingaruka mbi kw’isoko ry’imfungurwa”
 Mu Misiri, Lavrov yarijeje ko abashora intete hanze bazoshira mu ngiro ivyo “biyemeje”
 Ubutunzi bwa Misiri buragendera cane ku Burusiya gusumba ubw’ibindi bihugu vya Afrika bitari bike
 Hafi 80% y’ingano zayo zinjira mu gihugu ziva mu Burusiya na Ukraine, mu gihe ica gatatu c’ingenzi ziva hanze ari Abarusiya
 Uburusiya kandi bwatanguje umushinge wo kwubaka ikigo ca nikleyeri mu Misiri kizotwara imiriyaridi 26 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika
 Kuva kera, urudandaza hagati ya Moscou na Afrika rushingiye ku bijanye no kwivuna abansi – kuva ku nkoho gushika ku ndege z’intambara
 Ubu bwa vuba, abacangero b’abarusiya bararungitswe muri Mali na Centrafrique gufasha ingabo za reta kurwanya inyeshamba
 Mu rugendo rwiwe, Lavrov yarashimikiye ku nama ihuza Uburusiya na Afrika yiteze kubera muri Ethiopia mu kw’icumi, aho hashobora guterwa ibikumu ku masezerano mu vyo ubudandaji n’ukwivuna abansi mu ntumbero yo gukomeza ubucuti
 Uwundi nawe ari inyuma y’iwe ni intumwa idasanzwe ya Amerika mu karere k’ihembe rya Afrika Michael Hammer, na we nyene ariko aragendera Misiri na Ethiopia, mu gihe uwuserukira Amerika muri ONU, Linda Thomas-Greenfield na we yitezwe muri Uganda na Ghana mu ndwi iza
 Uburengero buripfuza cane kwiyerekana neza, hanyuma kumbure no kwibutsa ibihugu vya Afrika ko ari bwo butanga vyinshi mu buryo bw’urudandaza n’imfashanyo

Uburusiya bwakoze ibitero bikomeye mu bisagara vya Ukraine mu gihe Kyiv nayo iriko yongereza akariro mu kurondera kwisubiza akarere ka Kherson kari mu bumanuko
 Abantu batanu nibo bapfuye abandi 26 nabo barakomereka mu gihe ibisasu vya misire vyaterwa hagati mu gisagara ca Kropyvnytskyi, nk’uko abategetsi babivuga
 Abandi batatu nabo bapfuye mu gisagara ca Bakhmut kiri mu buseruko
 Hafi y’umugwa mukuru Kyiv, abantu batanu nibo bakomeretse mu gitero cabereye ku kigo ca gisirikare
 Eka n’uturere two mu buraruko n’ubumanuko bwa Ukraine natwo twatewe
 Ibi bibaye mu gihe Ukraine iriko irondera kuzibira ingabo z’Uburusiya ziri mu bumanuko
 Ikiraro gikomeye cinjira mu gisagara ca Kherson ntikigikora inyuma y’aho ingabo za Ukraine zigitereye na vya muzinga birasa kure vyatanzwe na Amerika
 Ibi bituma Uburusiya budashobora kurungika izindi ngabo n’ibindi birwanisho bukoresheje ikiraro ca Antonivsky
 Abategetsi bo mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi b’Ubwongereza bavuga ko iki gisagara conyene cafashwe mu ntango y’igitero c’Uburusiya ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2) ubu “catandukanijwe n’utundi turere twigaruriwe”
 Hagati aho, igisirikare ca Ukraine kiragabisha ko ubu Uburusiya buriko burakura ingabo ziri mu buseruko buzitwara mu bumanuko kurwanira intara ya Kherson
 Hari amasanamu yasohotse yerekana ingabo z’Uburusiya zigerageza kwubaka ikiraro c’igihe gito hafi y’icabomowe
 Kugenzura Kherson ni ikintu gikomeye ku Burusiya kuko ibufasha kuronka umuhora wo ku butaka winjira muri Crimea – izinga riri mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine ryigaruriwe na Kremlin mu 2014
 I Kropyvnytskyi – umugwa mukuru w’intara ya Kirovohrad – ishure ryigisha abadereva b’indege ryatewe misire zibiri ku wa kabiri, nk’uko umukuru w’iyo ntara Andriy Raikovych abimenyesha
 I Bakhmut, akarere kari mu buseruko bw’intara ya Donetsk, abantu n’imiburiburi batatu nibo bishwe abandi batatu nyene barakomereka igihe Uburusiya bwahacucagira ibibombe, nk’uko bitangazwa n’uwurongoye iyo ntara Pavlo Kyrylenko
 Inzu 12 zituwemwo n’abantu nazo nyene zononekaye
 Mu bindi vyabereye ahandi, abantu 15 bakomeretse igihe ibisasu vya misire z’Uburusiya zo mu bwoko bwa Kalibr vyaterwa ku kigo ca gisirikare i Liutizh, ku birometero vyababa cumi mu buraruko bwa Kyiv, nk’uko intwazangabo ya Ukraine Oleksiy Hromov abivuga
 Ntatomora nimba hari abapfuye
 Ahandi naho, umuntu umwe niwe yishwe abandi babiri barakomereka igihe Uburusiya bwatera amabombe mu ntara ya Dnipropetrovsk hagati utera uja mu buseruko, nk’uko abategetsi babivuga
 Inyuma y’amezi atanu Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya atanguye igitero muri Ukraine, ibihugu vy’uburengero bibandanya vyiyamiriza aka gasotoro ka Moscou
 Ejo ku wa kane, Amerika, Canada n’ibihugu 36 vya Bulaya vyavuze ko vyashinze umurwi w’abahinga wo kwihweza ingene ivy’agateka ka zina muntu vyifashe hagati mu Burusiya, aho bavuga ko ibintu vyayangaye kuva iki gitero gitanguye
 Biciye mw’ishirahamwe ry’umutekano n’ugufashanya i Bulaya (Organisation for Security and Cooperation in Europe, OSCE), ibi bihugu vyagiriza Moscou kubandanya bazivya amajwi yose anegura reta hagati mu gihugu
 Mw’itangazo vyasohoye, ibi bihugu vyerekana kandi impungenge yavyo ku makuru y’iyicarubozo rikorerwa mu mabohero
 Mu kw’icenda, aba bahinga bazosohora icegeranyo berekane n’ivyo abategetsi b’Uburusiya bakwiye gukora kugira ngo batorere umuti iki kibazo
 Nk’igihugu kimaze igihe kirekire mw’iri shirahamwe OSCE, Uburusiya bwari bwemeye gukurikiza ivyo bwiyemeje ku bijanye n’agateka ka zina muntu n’intwaro rusangi

Korea ya Ruguru iriteguye gukoresha inguvu zayo za nikleyeri mu kwirwanako, nk’uko indongozi yayo Kim Jong-un abivuga
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu birori vyo kwibuka Intambara ya Korea, Kim yongeyeko y’uko igihugu ciwe “citeguriye bihagije intambara ya gisirikare iyo ari yo yose” na Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, nk’uko bishikirizwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru rya reta, KCNA
 Aya majambo ashikirijwe mu gihe hari amakenga ko Korea ya Ruguru  yoba iriko irategura kugerageza ikindi gisasu ca nikleyeri ku ncuro igira indwi
 Mu kwezi guheze, Amerika yagabishije ko Pyongyang (umugwa mukuru wa Korea ya Ruguru) yashobora kugerageza iki gisasu umwanya uwo ari wo wose
 Korea ya Ruguru yaheruka kugerageza igisasu ca nikleyei mu 2017
 Ariko, icuka kibi kibandanya ciyongera muri iryo zinga rya Korea
 Intumwa idasanzwe ya Amerika muri Korea ya Ruguru Sung Kim avuga ko Korea ya Ruguru imaze kugerageza ibisasu vya misire bitari bike muri uno mwaka – 31 ugereranije na 25 yagerageje mu mwaka wose wa 2019 uzwi ko ari wo mwaka yaherukirako kugerageza ibirwanisho vyinshi
 Mu kwa gatandatu, Korea y’Epfo yaciye yihora mu kugerageza ibisasu umunani vyayo vya misire
 N’aho intambara ya Korea yabaye hagati ya 1950 na 1953 yarangiye habaye amasezerano y’agahengwe, Korea ya Ruguru ifata ko aya masezerano ari intsinzi yayo kuri Amerika
 Ibirori vyo kwibuka intsinzi bihimbazwa buri mwaka n’amadefire ya gisirikare, intambo n’imiriro y’umunezero
 Mw’ijambo ryiwe yashikirije mu guhimbaza uwo musi, Kim yavuze ko ivyago vya nikleyeri biterwa na Amerika bisaba ko Korea ya Ruguru ishika ku “gikorwa cayo cihutirwa” co gukomeza urwego rwo kwivuna abansi
 Yongerako y’uko Amerika ifata ukutari ko imyimenyerezo ya gisirikare, aho iyifata nk’agasomborotso
 Kim kandi asa n’uwuvuga ku makuru avuga ko Korea y’Epfo iriko irarondera kunagura integuro yo kwitanga igitero ca nikleyeri gishobora gukorwa na Korea ya Ruguru, mu gutegura ibitero vyo kwikingira mu gihe horamuka himirije igitero
 Iyi nteguro izwi nka "Kill Chain", yateguwe ubwa mbere imyaka cumi iheze, isaba ko haba ibitero vyo kwitanga misire za Pyongyang kandi mu gihe vyoshoboka n’abategetsi bayo bakuru
 Bamwe mu bahinga baragabisha ko ibi bifise inkurikizi zavyo kandi ko bishobora gutuma haba ugusiganwa mu kwegeranya ibirwanisho
 Muri ibi birori vyo kwibuka intsinzi, Kim avuga ko reta n’igisirikare vya Perezida Yoon Suk-yeol wa Korea y’Epfo bishobora “kuzimanganywa” mu gihe yoramuka akoze ibitero vyo kwitanga Korea ya Ruguru
 Umwihwezo wa Rupert Wingfield-Hayes, BBC News Amajambo ya Kim Jong-Un yo kugabisha ko akarere ka Korea gashobora kuba “kari mu kwinjira mu ntambara” ni ibintu biteye ubwoba cane
 Ariko amajambo ya Korea ya Ruguru akunze kuba ayo guturira, cane cane ku bakeba bakomeye
 Ibi vyerekana ingene ubutegetsi bwa Korea ya Ruguru bushavuriye umukuru w’igihugu mushasha wa Korea y’Epfo Yoon Suk-yeol
 Kuva afashe ubutegetsi mu kwa gatanu, Perezida Yoon yashikirije poritike nshasha ikaze yo kwirwanako
 Izoshobora guha uruhusha ingabo za Korea y’Epfo gukora ibitero vyo kwitanga Korea ya Ruguru, mu gihe Seoul izoba ibona ko ishobora guterwa na Pyongyang ikoresheje ibirwansiho vya nikleyeri
 Iyi nteguro izwi nka "Kill Chain" ishobora kwemerera Korea y’Epfo gukora ibitero vyo kwitanga vya misire n’ivy’indege ku nyungu za Korea ya Ruguru, harimwo n’ibigo vy’intwazangabo n’igenzura vya gisirikare vya Korea ya Ruguru
 Mu yandi majambo, kugerageza kwica Kim Jong-Un we nyene
 Pyongyang ntiyishimiye kandi ingene Washington yigize sindabibazwa kuva Perezida iden asubiriye Donald Trump
 Ibi vyose bishobora kwerekana ko turiko tugana ahantu dushobora kubona Korea ya Ruguru yunyuye ibintu n’ibigirankana
 Ubu abantu bose biteze ko Pyongyang igiye gukora igerageza ry'igisasu ca nikleyeri gitererwa mu kuzimu ku ncuro igira indwi
 Imyiteguro irabandanya kuva mu kwa gatatu ku kigo c’igerageza kiri ahitwa Punggye-ri

Ishirahamwe riharanira agateka ka zina muntu mu Burundi IDHB (Initiative pour les Droits de l'Homme au Burundi) ryagiriza ico gihugu kurungika abasirikare n'imbonerakure muri Republika ya Demokrasi ya Congo, RDC, kugwanya umuhari wa RED-TABARA
 Ico cegeranyo ciswe "Igikorwa co kwiyoberanya, ubutumwa bw'Uburundi mw'ibanga muri Congo" kivuga ko abo basirikare n'imbonerakure begeranirizwa mu makambi atatu ya gisirikare imbere yo kurungikwa muri RD Congo mw'ijoro
 Ishirahamwe IDHB rivuga ko ivyo bikorwa vyoba bifise inkomoko ku ngendo z'abakuru b'ivyo bihugu bibiri, Uburundi na RD Congo, bagiriraniye, aho hashizwe umukono ku masezerano yo gufashanya muvyo umutekano ariko atasiguwe neza mw'ido n'ido
 Mu rugendo prezida Evariste Ndayishimiye yagize muri RD Congo mu kwezi kw'indwi umwaka uheze yavuze ko baganiriye na mugenziwe Felix Tshisekedi ingene "hotuzwa" imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho iri mu buseruko bwa RD Congo
 Igihe yaza kumusubiriza mu ndumane mu rugendo yagize i Bujumbura mu kwezi kwa gatanu mu 2022, Tshisekedi yagize ati:"Ni ngombwa ko hongerezwa inguvu mu gukizura no mu bikorwa vya gisirikare n'umutekano ibihugu vyose bihuriyeko
" Iryo shirahamwe rivuga ko ari muri iyo ntumbero abasirikare b'abarundi n'imbonerakure bashika 700 bamaze kurungikwa muri RD Congo kuva mu mpera z'umwaka uheze
 IDHB ivuga kandi ko ico gikorwa gifashwe mu mugongo n'umugambwe uri ku butegetsi wa CNDD-FDD, ari na co gituma badapfa uwo bakirungitsemwo
 Ico cegeranyo kigira giti:"Imbonerakure zegeranywa n'abategetsi hagati mu gihugu kandi ntizibwirwa iyo ziba ziroye
 "Haba mu basirikare canke mu mbonerakure, bahitamwo abo babona biyumvamwo umugambwe CNDD-FDD
" Ariko kiragaruka kikavuga ko, barondeye n'abahoze mu gisirikare ca kera bajana muri ivyo bikorwa vya gisirikare muri RD Congo, ariko ngo si benshi ku bwoba ko bohava baca batorokera mu muhari wa RED-TABARA bagiye kugwanya
 Umukuru w'umugambwe uri ku butegetsi, Reverien Ndikuriyo aradomwako urutoke
 Imbonerakure imwe yagiye muri ivyo bikorwa, imwagiriza ko mu nama yigeze kubagirisha yababajije ati:"Igihugu coterwa, muriteguye kukigwanira? Bose ngo bishuye ego batinya ko bahakanye boca bafatwa nk'abatavuga rumwe na reta
 Iyindi mbonerakure yemeza ko yahuriye n'uwurongoye urwo rwego mu gihugu cose, Sylvestre Ndayize, mu ngoro y'umugambwe CNDD-FDD aho yamubwiye ko agira amurungike ahantu kuko yaciye mu gisirikare
 Agira ati:"Mu nyuma yaransavye nimero za telefone nca mbona andungikiye ibihumbi ijana, ambwira ko ndayasiga muhira, ko bazompa ayo nzokoresha nitwagenda
" Abandanya avuga ko yagiye kumenya ko agiye muri RD Congo bahuriye n'izindi mbonerakure 90 hamwe n'abasirikare mw'ikambi ya Camp Chinois iri i Kabezi
 IDHB kandi bagiriza umugambwe  CNDD-FDD gutegura ibikorwa bibi bafatiye kw'ijambo ryashikirijwe n'umukuru w'uwo mugambwe Reverien Ndikuriyo yavuze ko "gushika mu 2025 hoba hamaze guhabwa inyigisho nkarishwabwenge imbonerakure zishika 24
000
" Iryo shirahamwe rikaba ribona ko izo nyigisho zijanye no kwitegurira amatora yo mu 2025 hamwe na 2027 Nyinshi mu mbonerakure zimaze kuja muri RD Congo ziva mu ntara za Bujumbura, Bubanza, Cibitoke, Gitega, Kayanza, Kirundo, Muramvya, Muyinga na Ngozi
 Ico cegeranyo ca IDHB kivuga ko abari kw'isonga mu gutegura ivyo bikorwa vya gisirikare muri RD Congo, ari abakozi b'iperereza Alfred Innocent Museremu na Niyonzima Mathias batazira Kazungu
 Museremu ngo ni we yabazaniye impuzu z'igipolisi hamwe n'ibirato vya plastique, bahabwa itegeko ko muri izo mpuzu bambara ishati gusa canke ipantaro gusa
 Kazungu we avugwa mu nteguro mu manama menshi yabereye muri RD Congo
 Kibandanya kivuga ko abahirahiriye bakabaza igituma bari muri RD congo baca bicwa - izo nkuru ariko ngo bakaba badashobora kuzemeza
 Haravugwa abashika 40 boba barishwe bazira kwanka kuja muri ubwo butumwa bwo muri RD Congo, aho basaba ko babereka urupapuro rubarungika muri ubwo butumwa
 Abaja muri ivyo bikorwa kandi ngo babanza kwakwa ibibaranga n'amaterefone ngendanwa kugira ntibahave bamena ibanga
 Rimwe na rimwe imiryango y'abapfiriye muri RD Congo ntibahabwa uburenganzira bwo kugira imigirwa ijanye n'urupfu
 Ico cegeranyo kivuga ko muri iyo ntambara ihuza abasirikare b'Uburundi n'umuhari wa RED - TABARA ku butaka bwa RD Congo, bafashwa n'imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho yo muri ico gihugu nka Mai Mai Kijangala na Gumino
 Twagerageje kurondera abategetsi b'Uburundi kugira bagire ico bavuze kuri iki cegeranyo ariko ntiturabaronka

Umugabo asanzwe agendana umugera wa VIH utera SIDA kuva mu myaka ya 1980 aboneka ko yakize, akaba abaye uwa kane gusa, nk’uko bivugwa n’abaganga
 Yatewe umusokoro wo mw’igufa ariko aravurwa indwara ya kanseri yo mu maraso yo mu bwoko bwa leukaemia, awuhawe n’umugiraneza asanzwe adafatwa n’umugera
 Uyu mugabo w’imyaka 66 atashatse ko izina ryiwe rimenyekana, yarahagaritse gufata imiti yari amaze imyaka irenga 30 afata, yo gupfupfahaza VIH
 Avuga ko afise “umunezero utagira urugero” kubona ata mugera agifise mu mubiri
 Uyu mugabo azwi nk’umurwayi w’“Igisagara c’Umwizero” (City of Hope) inyuma y’ibitaro yariko aravurirwamwo vya Duarte mu ntara ya California
 Abenshi mu bagenzi biwe bahitanywe na SIDA  imbere y’uko imiti yo gupfupfahaza itangura guhabwa abarwayi mu ntumbero yo kubafasha kubandanya babaho ubuzuma busanzwe
 Umugera HIV/VIH (Virus de l'Immunodéficience Humaine), wica abasoda b’umubiri bigatuma umuntu arwara indwara ya SIDA kuko umubiri ntuba ugishoboye kurwanya umugera
 Mw’itangazo, uyu mugabo avuga ati: "Igihe bantora umugera mu 1988, co kimwe n’abandi, nibajije ko nciriwe urwo gupfa
 "Sinigeze nibaza ko noshoboye kubandanya mbaho gushika aho mbona umusi ntazoba ngifise umugera”
 Ariko, ntiyakize ngo ni uko yavuwe umugera wa VIH, ahubwo vyarahuriranye kuko yariko aravurwa kanseri yo mu maraso yo mu bwoko bwa leukaemia yari yanduye afise imyaka 63
 Abaganga bamukurikirana ico gihe bafashe ingingo ko yoterwa umusokoro mu ntumbero yo gusubiriza uturemangingo tw’amaraso twari dufise kanseri
 Rero yagize amahirwe asanga umugiraneza yemeye kumuha utu turemangingo ari mu murwi wa ba bantu batandura umugera wa VIH
 Umugera winjirira mu turemangingo twera (globules blancs/ white blood cells) tw’amaraso uciye mu muhora utaboneka n’amaso, indemamubiri (proteine) izwi nka CCR5
 Hagati aho, hariho abantu, harimwo n’uyu mugiraneza yamuhaye utu turemangingo, bafise iyi CCR5 igenda ihindagurika ikazibira uwu muhora, bigatuma umugera udashobora kwinjira
 Uyu murwayi 'w’Igisagara c’Umwizero' yarakurikiraniwe hagufi inyuma yo guterwa utu turemangino, haragera igihe umugera utakiboneka mu mubiri
 Amaze amezi arenga 17 ata mugera umurimwo
 Dr Jana Dickter, umuganga avura indwara ziterwa n’imigera kw’ico Gisagara c’Umwizero, avuga ati: "Wari umunezero kuri twebwe kumubwira ko umugera wa SIDA utakiri muri we kandi ko bitari bikenewe ko abandanya afata imiti yo gupfupfahaza yari amaze imyaka irenga 30 afata”
 Ikintu nk’iki cabaye ubwa mbere mu 2011 igihe Timothy Ray Brown – azwi nk’umurwayi w’i Berlin – aba umuntu wa mbere kw’isi yakize umugera wa SIDA
 Mu myaka itatu iheze, hamaze kuba abandi bantu batatu bakira muri ubu buryo
 Uyu murwayi w’Igisagara c’Umwizero ni we muntu wa mbere afise imyaka myinshi avuwe muri ubu buryo akongera akaba n’uwa mbere amaze igihe kirekire agendana VIH ashoboye gukira
 Hagati aho, guterwa imisokoro ntibisigura ko bigiye guhindura ibintu mu kuvura imiriyoni 38 z’abantu bagendana SIDA muri kino gihe
 Dr Dickter avuga ati: "Ni uburyo bugoye cane kandi bushobora kugira ingaruka mbi zikomeye
 Rero si inzira nyayo yo kuvura abantu bose bagendana SIDA”
 Hagati aho, abashakashatsi bariko bararondera ingene bokwibanda kuri uwu muhora w’indemamubiri CCR5 mu gutera uturemangino nk’imwe mu nzira yo kuvura umugera
 Ubu buryo bwarashikirijwe mu nama yerekeye SIDA yabaye mu 2022 i Montreal muri Canada
 Avuga ku vyavuye muri ubu bushakashatsi Prof Sharon Lewin aherutse gutorwa ngo arongore ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryishinze kurwanya umugera wa SIDA, International Aids Society, avuga ati: "Umuti uracari kananirabahinga mu bushakashatsi kuri SIDA”
 Avuga ko “imbere y’aha habaye abantu bake bakize” bagatanga “icizere kibandanya ku bantu bagendana umugera wa SIDA,  ndetse inaha umwizero abahinga”

Umukuru w’igihugu c’Ubufaransa Emmanuel Macron aranegura bikomeye inyifato y’abategetsi ba Afrika ku ntambara ya Ukraine, hari mu kiganiro yahaye abamenyeshamakuru i Yaoundé muri Cameroun
 Macron ariyamiriza "uburyarya, cane cane ku mugabane wa Afrika” buhakana ko amatati ya Ukraine ari intambara
 Ibihugu bimwe vya Afrika vyaririnze kunegura ku mugaragaro igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine
 Mu kwa gatatu, ibihugu 17 vyaranse kwerekana aho bihagaze mu matora ya ONU yo kwiyamiriza iki gitero
 Avuga kandi ko inyishu yonyene ku kibazo c’akarere ka Cameroun gakoresha icongereza ari ukwegereza ubutegetsi abanyagihugu (decentralisation)
 Ikinyamakuru kitegamiye reta, Journal du Cameroun, gikorera ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi canditse gisubiramwo Macron, aho avuga ati: "Ni iyi nzira ya poritike yo kuganira no gutunganya gushasha ubutegetsi bw’igihugu ishobora gutorera umuti urama iki kibazo”
 Yavuze ivyo ari kumwe n’umukuru w’igihugu ca Cameroun, Paul Biya, i Yaoundé
 Nk’uko ikinyamakuru Journal du Cameroun kibivuga, aba bategetsi bompi bavuganye kandi ku “kibazo c’abarwanyi ba Boko Haram biyitirira idini rya Islam bagisibije mu buraruko bwa Cameroun", hamwe n’intambara hagati y’ingabo za Cameroun n’inyeshamba zirondera kwiyonkora
 Umukuru w’igihugu c’Ubufaransa yatanguye urugendo mu bihugu bitatu vya Afrika ku wa 25 Mukakaro (7), aho ibibazo vy’ubukene bw’imfungurwa, imishamirano iterwa n’inyeshamba ziyitirira idini rya Islam n’imigenderanire hagati y’Ubufaransa n’uyu mugabane vyitezwe kwizizira ibiganiro azogiriranira n’abategetsi ba Afrika

Ubushikiranganji bw'intwaro yo hagati mu gihugu n'umutekano bumenyesha ko ibitungwa bigiye gusubira kubagwa kuva ku musi wa gatatu w'indwi iza
 Ivyo vyashikirijwe n'umunyamabanga ntayegayezwa Martin Niteretse mu nama yagiranye n'abarongoye intara, abarongoye uturere mu gipolisi hamwe n'abajejwe uburimyi n'ubworozi mu ntara
 Ingingo yo guhagarika kubaga ibitungwa yari yafashwe kubera iyaduka ry'ingwara y'inyonko yo mu kiyaya ca Rift (Fièvre de la vallée du Rift) Kugira ivyo bishoboke ngo ibitungwa vyo kubagwa bitegerezwa kwegeranirizwa hamwe
 Agira ati:"Abayangayanga  bakeneye kuzobaga mubatunganirize aho begeraniriza ibitungwa bashaka kuzobaga mu ndwi iza
 "Nta nka izobagwa itavuye aho muri ico kibanza
 Kuko ntayizova mu muhana ica ija kubagwa ubwo nyene
" Ivyo bitungwa kugira bije kubagwa, bitegerezwa kumara imisi indwi biri mu kibanza categekanijwe mu makomine yose, bigenzurwa ko bitagwaye
 Martin Niteretse kandi avuga ko ata nyama izova mw'ikomine zija mu yindi
 Nta n'inka zirekuriwe kuvanwa mu ntara zija mu yindi, kiretse ngo izijanywe kubagirwa mu gisagara c'ubutunzi ca Bujumbura
 Ariko ngo nko mu ntara zitagira inka nyinshi, abayangayanga baho barashobora kuja kuzigura ahandi, ariko abategetsi b'aho baziguze bategerezwa kubaha urupapuro ruziherekeza
 Kandi ico gihe zizoca ziherekezwa n'igipolisi kugira ntihagire izururukira mu nzira canke izuririra mu nzira  zitagenzuwe neza
 Icipfuzo ngo n'uko mu ndwi iza hatangura kubagwa inka, hamwe n'impene n'intamaba 'bishobotse'
 Abadandaza basabwe kandi kudaca bikika mu kiza ngo baduze ibiciro
 Ku bijanye n'urucanco, Martin Niteretse yabasavye kuja gutegura abajejwe ako kazi kugira incanco zishitse bace baja ku kivi
 Haraheze amezi arenga abiri hatanzwe itegeko ko kizira kikaziririza kubaga inka, impene n'intama, mu ntumbero yo gukumira inyono yo mu kiyaya ca Rift

Reta y’Uburundi itera akamo abanyagihugu kubandanya bakurikiza amabwirizwa yo kwirinda ikiza karanda ca Covid-19 kuko “ibiharuro vy’abantu batorwa Covid-19 vyongerekanye”
 Inyuma y’inama yahuje abajejwe kurwanya iki kiza ejo ku wa kabiri 26 Mukakaro (7) 2022, umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu Sylvie Nzeyimana yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru ko haheze “ikiringo nk’ico indwi zitatu … dusanga nko ku musi hatorwa abantu bashika 200” baba baranduye mu baba bipimishije
 Ati: “Ico kiza kiracariho, kirirabika ariko iyo dusamaye ntidukurikize impanuro zo kwigikngira, gica kigaruka kikaduhwibira, abantu bakandura”
 Umushikiranganji Nzeyimana ntatanga ibiharuro vy’abapimwa buri musi ariko avuga ko ibiharuro vy’abandura vyiyongereye ugereranije n’ingene vyari bimeze inyuma y’amezi atari make vyari vyaragabanutse cane
 Mu ntara ntara zigeramiwe nk’uko abimenyesha harimwo igisagara ca Bujumbura, intara za Bujumbura, Gitega, Bururi mu bunamuko bw’igihugu, Muyinga na Kirundo mu buraruko
 Sylvie Nzeyimana avuga kandi ko hari n’abinjira bavuye hanze bapimwa bagasanga baranduye
 Ati: “Muri ino misi, abapimwa ku mipaka Uburundi busangiye n’ibindi bihugu, harimwo no ku kibuga c’indege, twasanze ko ingenzi ziza ziciye mu ndege harimwo abatari bake baza barwaye … aho nk’akarorero mu ndwi yose iheze, abashika 80 barapimwe basanga bararwaye uwo mugera”
 Abinjiye mu gihugu bategerezwa gupimwa
 Abasaba kwihutira kuraba inyishu hanyuma basanze barwaye bakitura amavuriro bwango
 Nta ngingo ruhasha zifatirwa abinjira bavuye hanze nk’uko vyigeze kuba muri kahise
 Igicapo cerekana ingene iki kiza cifashe mu gihugu cerekana ko ku bantu 7
483 bapimwe ku magenekerezo ya 23, 24 na 25 uku kw’indwi, 423 basanze baranduye, muri bo 39 bakaba bari bavuye hanze
 Ibiharuro bitangwa n’ishami rijejwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi OMS/WHO vyerekana ko mu Burundi abantu 44
437 aribo bamaze kwandura,  kuva iki kiza gishika mu gihugu mu 2020, 15  bakaba ari co gitigiri OMS yahawe c'abamaze  gupfa
 Ibi biharuro vyarakemanzwe n’ammwe mu shirahamwe ategamiye kuri leta ko bitavuga ukuri kw’ingene Covid yari yifashe mu gihugu
 Ibiharuro kandi vyerekana ko abagera kuri 0,1 % bonyene nibo bamaze kwicandagisha mu gihugu

Igisata c’Uburusiya kijejwe igendereza FSB kivuga ko cashoboye gutesha igendereza rya Ukraine ryariko rigerageza kunyuruza n’imiburiburi indege zitatu za gisirikare z’Uburusiya
 Umunyamakuru Khristo Grozev akora amakuru y’igendereza akaba yagirizwa n’iki gisata c’Uburusiya kijejwe umutekano ko yafashije Kyiv, avuga ko yari azi iki gikorwa
 Nk’uko abivuga, FSB yakoze “ikosa rikomeye” mu gushira ahabona “indangamuntu z’abakozi batari bake bakora mw’igendereza”, Bellingcat (ikinyamakuru gikorera ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi gitanga amakuru y’igendereza, kikaba carirukanywe mu Burusiya cagirizwa ko “gikorera abanyamahanga”) caranditse ibi vyose
 BBC yegeranije ibintu vyose bwizwi kuri iki
 Ku wa mbere mu gitondo, ikigo ca FSB kijejwe imibano kivuga ko abajejwe igendereza bashoboye gutesha abajejwe igendereza ba Ukraine bariko bagerageza kunyuruza indege Su-24 itera amabombe
 Su-34 itera amabombe kandi iri muri za ndege zinyaruka gusumba ijwi, hamwe na Tu-22M3 itera ibisasu vya misire mu gihe zari ku bikorwa
 Nk’uko bivugwa na FSB, igisata kijejwe igendereza ca Ukraine cari cemereye buri mudereva ko yari kuronswa imiriyoni zishika zibiri z’amadorari y’abanyamerika mu gihe abagore babo nabo bagaca barungikwa mu bihugu vy’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya
 FSB yasohoye videwo irimwo aba badereva berekana indege zabo kandi bafise mu minwe impapuro ziriko ibiharuro
 Nk’uko iki gisata kibivuga, aba badereva basabwe n’igisata kijejwe igendereza ca Ukraine kwifata videwo kugira bemeze ko bari biteguriye inyuruzwa ry’izi ndege
 Aba badereva bategerezwa gushira inyuma y’izi ndege za gisirikare ibiharuro bari bahawe n’abajejwe igendereza ba Ukraine
 Nk’uko bibandanya bivugwa na FSB, muri iki gikorwa, urwego rw’Uburusiya rujejwe igendereza rwarashoboye guhatira igisirikare ca Ukraine gushira ahabona intunganyo y’igisata ca gisirikare kirwanira mu kirere be n’ibibuga vy’indege mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine
 Mu kurangiza, FSB ivuga ko Ukraine yakoze ibi “ifashwe mu mugongo n’ibisata bijejwe igendereza vy’ibihugu vy’Uburengero, cane cane Ubwongereza”
 Abategetsi b’urwego rw’Uburusiya rujejwe igendereza bemeza ko umunyamakuru Khristo Grozev akora amakuru y’igendereza mu kinyamakuru Bellingcat yagize uruhara muri ico gikorwa
 FSB imwagiriza ko akorana n’igisata Mi-6 c’Ubwongereza kijejwe igendereza
 Aciye ku rubuguga rwa Twitter, Grozev we nyene ubwiwe aremeza ko igikorwa nk’iki cakozwe n’igisata kijejwe igendereza ca Ukraine, ariko akavuga ko we ubwiwe ata ruhara yabigizemwo
 Mu kwa kane 2022,  inama nshingamateka ya Ukraine (Verkhovna Rada) yaremeje itegeko ryo guha agashirukabute umuntu azozana igikoresho ca gisirikare c’Uburusiya ku gushaka kwiwe
 Nk’akarorero, umusirikare w’Uburusiya ashobora guhabwa amadorari 100
000 mu gihe yoramuka ahaye Kyiv ikimodoka ntamenwa (char/tank), hamwe n’umuriyoni w’amadorari ku wotanga indege
 Inyuma y’aha, nk’uko bivugwa na Grozev, ibisata vya Ukraine bijejwe umutekano niho vyaciye bifata ingingo yo kwegera abadereva b’Uburusiya babasaba kunyuruza indege bazoba bahawe n’Uburusiya
 Abanyamakuru ba Bellingcat barabonye ibi baca batangura gukora ireresi
 Ati: "Twafashe amasanamu ‘y’ibiganiro’ hagati y’abari bajejwe kurondera aba badereva n'aba badereva nyene vyari vyatanguye nk’uko vyari vyitezwe
 "Ariko imvugo zabo ntizatevye guhinduka, aho vyaboneka ko aba badereva batari bakivuga ku giti cabo, ariko ko bagendera ku mategeko, bishoboka ko ari ayo bahabwa n’abakuru ba FSB”
 Uruhande rwa Ukraine rwariketse ko hari ikintu kitariko kigenda neza igihe umwe mu badereva yasavye ko umuhabara wiwe ari we yojanwa hanze, hako hajanwa umugore wiwe, nk’uko Grozev abivuga
 Hamaze kuba amatohoza, uyu munayamakuru yagiye gutora ko uyo mugore ashobora kuba yarakoranye na FSB mu gihe kanaka
 “Ico gihe, naciye mbona neza ko iki gikorwa cari capfuye ahubwo kigahindukamwo “ugucengana”, aho buri ruhande rwagerageza kurondera amakuru yose ashoboka yo ku rundi ruhande, mu gihe narwo rwakora uko rushoboye kwose mu gutanga amakuru atari yo”, nk’uko vyandikwa na Grozev
 Nk’uko uyu munyamakuru akora amakuru y’igendereza abivuga, ico gihe Ukraine yaciye itangura guha aba badereva amakuru atari yo ku kungene abasirikare barwanira mu kirere bagiye kurungikwa ku rubuga, hanyuma aba badereva nabo, baca baha Kyiv amakuru y’ingene bazokwururuka n'ingene bazoshika i Kyiv
 Kumbure navyo vyari ibinyoma
 Nk’uko Grozev abivuga, uwu mukino w’igendereza warangiye igihe umugore w’umwe muri abo badereva, ari kumwe n’umurwi w’abakozi ba FSB, bafata urugendo bakaja i Misnk (umugwa mukuru wa Biélorussie/Belarus mu ntumbero yo kubonana n’abajejwe igendereza ba Ukraine
 Nta n’umwe yaje muri iyi nama
 Aho niho impande zompi zaciye zibona ko ata cizere cari kihari ko bashobora kuronka amakuru nyayo ava kuri buri ruhande
 Igisata ca Ukraine kijejwe igendereza ntaco cashikirije haba ku bivugwa na FSB canke na Grozev

