Ku mbuga hwaniro, uyu mugore wo mu Buhindi atereka ubwana bwiwe arashimirwa ariko kandi akanegurwa n’abantu
 Ariko wewe avuga ko adahungabanywa n’ibivugwa vyose ku bwanwa bwiwe
 "Ndakunda ubwanwa bwanje," Shyja w’imyaka 35 niko yanditse kuri WhatsApp, musi y’ifoto yiwe
 Yama abazwa – n’abantu babona amafoto yiwe ku rubuga rwa Facebook canke bahura nawe amaso mu yandi – igituma atereka ubwanwa
 Avuga ati: “Ikintu conyene novuga ni uko gusa ndabukunda
 Cane”
 Shyja, izina ryonyene akoresha, aba mu karere ka Kannur  mu ntara yo Kerala iri mu bumanuko bw’Ubuhindi
 Nk’uko bimeze ku bagore batari bake, yaramaze imyaka itari mike atsiba ubwana bwiwe bwo hejuru
 Mu gihe yama amwa ingohe ziwe, Shyja avuga ko atigeze yumva ko akeneye kumwa ubwanwa bwiwe bwo hejuru
 Mu myaka itanu iheze, bwatanguye kuba bwinshi buboneka neza kandi Shyja arabureka abinezererewe cane
 Ati: "Ubu si mbona ko noshobora kubaho ntabufise
 Igihe ikiza ca Covid gitangura, naranka kwambara agapfukamunwa igihe cose kubera kanzibira isura”
 Abantu benshi bamubona bamusaba ko yokwikurako ubu bwanwa bwo hejuru ariko Shyja ntavyumva
 "Sinigeze numva ko ndi mubi kubera ndabufise canke ko ari ikintu ntategerezwa kuba mfise”
 Abagore bama babwirwa ko imishatsi yo kw’isura atari myiza kuri bo, ko rero botanga amafaranga kugira ngo bayibakure – canke bakayigabanya – igihe cose
 Amahinguriro akora imiti yo kubuza imishatsi kumera aregeranya amamiriyaridi n’amamiriyaridi y’amadorari mu gukora amavuta, inzembe n’ibindi bishobora kurandurana n’imizi imishatsi, bigurwa n’abagore bashoboye kubigura
 Ariko muri ino myaka ya vuba, abagore benshi bahisemwo kwemera mbere no kwishimira ubu bwanwa
 Mu 2016, Harnaam Kaur aharanira ukwiyemera kw’umuntu uko aba ameze kwose (Body positive body positivity) yabaye umugore wa mbere akiri muto kw’isi yose yameze ubwanwa ku munwa wose no kw’itama nk’umugabo, nk’uko bivugwa n’ikigo Guinness World Records
 Mu biganiro yagiye atanga, yamye avuga ukungene ukwemera ubwanwa bwiwe kwabaye igihe gikomeye co kwiyemera imbere y’abamuzomera
 Ku bwa Shyja, gutereka ubwanwa si ikintu umuntu afatira, ni kimwe mu bigize ubuzima bwiwe
 Ati: "Jewe nkora ico nshatse
 Iyaba nari mfise ubuzima bubiri, kumbure bumwe nari kububamwo uko abandi bashaka”
 Kimwe mu vyatumye afata iyi ngendo ni ibibazo vy’amagara yahanganye navyo mu myaka itari mike
 Shyja baramubaze  incuro zitandatu mu myaka cumi – rimwe kwari ukugira bamukure ikivyimba mw’ibere, irindi naryo kwari ukumukura utuvyimba mu gasaho k’imbuto
 Aho aherukira kubagwa, kwari ukumukuramwo igitereko, haraciye imyaka itanu
 Ati: "Igihe cose baheza kumbaga, naguma nizeye ko ntari gusubira muri ico cumba c’ibagiro”
 Kubona yashoboye kurengana ibi bibazo vyose vy’amagara vyakomeje ivyiyumviro vya Shyja  ko ari ngombwa ko abaho mu buzima bwiwe bumuha umunezero
 Shyja avuga ko akiri umwana yari afise isoni
 Ni gake abagore mu kigwati ciwe bashobora kuboneka hanze inyuma y’isaha cumi na zibiri z’umugoroba
 N’aho Kerala ari imwe mu ntara z’Ubuhindi zigenda zibaho ubuzima bwa none, kandi zifise ibimenyetso bikomeye vy’iterambere, mu turere twinshi umugabo ni we afise ijambo rya nyuma, kandi abagore bama babuzwa gufata ingendo canke kwibana
 Igihe arongorwa akimukira mu ntara ya Tamil Nadu ihana urubibe n’iyo yavukiyemwo, Shyja avuga ko yaryohewe no kubona ubundi bwisanzure bushasha
 Avuga ati: "Umugabo wanje yarashobora kuja ku kazi akagaruka atevye
 Rero narashobora kwicara hanze ku mugoroba, rimwe na rimwe nkaja no kw’iduka ndi umwe mw’ijoro iyo hari ico nkeneye
 Nta n’umwe yavyitaho
 Igihe niga gukora ibintu jenyene, vyankomereje ukwiyemera”
 Avuga kandi ko ariko aragerageza kuvyigisha umukobwa wiwe w’umuyabaga
 Umuryango wa Shyja n’incuti ziwe bamye bamushigikira kuri buno bwanwa bwiwe
 Umukobwa wiwe amubwira ko bumubereye
 Ariko Shyja avuga ko yabwiwe amajambo y’ubwoko bwose avugwa n’abantu iyo bamubonye kw’ibarabara
 Ati: "Abantu barantwenga bavuga ngo ‘abagabo bonyene nibo bamera ubwanwa, kubera iki umugore yobumera’?” Mu myaka itari mike, ni kenshi yagiye avugwa mu binyamakuru vyo muri ico gihugu
 Mu misi iheze, nk’uko abivuga, yarabonye amajambo y’agahemo yanditswe ku nkuru yamuvuga yari yacishijwe ku rubuga rwa Facebook n’ikinyamakuru co muri ico gihugu
 Umuntu umwe yabajije igituma atari gufata urwembwe akamwa ubwanwa bwiwe bimaze kuboneka ko ingohe ziwe yari yazimoye
 Ati:"Ariko si ikibazo kijanye n’ivyo nshaka – none ngumye iki hanyuma nikureko iki?” Abagenzi ba Shyja akenshi bishurana agashavu kuri ano majambo yandikwa kuri Facebook, ariko avuga ko ivyo ataco bimubwiye na gato
 "Mu bisanzwe, kenshi ndabaraba nkabatwenga”

Sentare yo mu Bushinwa yafashe ingingo yo gutsindisha umugore atarongowe ariko arondera ko amagi yiwe y’ubuvyeyi abikwa ahantu kugira azoyakoreshe muri kazoza
 Teresa Xu yuguruje urubanza mu 2019 inyuma y’uko ibitaro bijejwe irondoka ry’abagore  ku mugwa mukuru Pékin/ Beijing (Beijing Obstetrics and Gynaecology Hospital) vyankiye kubimukorera, kuko bisanzwe bikorerwa abagore bubatse mugabo bakaba bafise ingorane z’ubugumba
 Ariko sentare yasanze ibi bitaro ata burenganzira bwiwe vyahonyanze
 Uyu mugore Xu avuga ko iyi ngingo ya sentare ari "inzitizi" ku burenganzira bw’abagore ku bijanye n’irondoka, akaba yiyemeje kwunguruza
 Nk’uko iyi ngingo ibivuga, ibi bitaro bivuga ko vyatahuye akababaro k’uyu mugore ariko ko vyategerezwa gukurikiza amategeko
 Igihe Xu yuguruza urubanza ubwa mbere, Chao Wei, umuvugizi w’ibi bitaro, yavuze ko abakozi bakurikije amategeko ya reta ku bijanye n’ugufasha mw’irondoka hakoreshejwe ubuhinga bwa none, nk’uko ikinyamakuru New York Times kivyandika
 Xu, ico gihe yari afise imyaka 30, yari yagerageje kubikisha imbuto ziwe z’ubuvyeyi mu 2018 kugira ngo yiteho akazi kiwe nk’umwanditsi yigenga
 Ariko avuga ko abakozi b’ivyo bitaro bamuhimirije ko ahubwo yorondera umwana ico gihe
 Mu nyuma yabwiwe ko ubu bufasha buhabwa gusa abagore badashobora gusama imbanyi hadakoreshejwe ubuhinga, nk’uko vyandikwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP
 Ibi bitaro bivuga kandi ko imbanyi ku bagore bakuze cane ishobora guteza ingorane gusumba, bikerekana kandi n’ibibazo abagore bibana bakunze kugira
 Amagi y’abagore agenda atakaza inguvu uko imyaka igenda yiyongera, bigatuma bitoroha kuronka umwana
 Abagore basaba ubu bufasha bwo kubikisha imbuto mu Bushinwa bagenda biyongera, abenshi mu bagore bifise, bashoboye kwirihira, bakaja hanze kugira babikorerwe
 Xu avuga ko yiyumviriye kuja hanze, ariko agasanga birazimvye cane
 Urubanza rwiwe rwarakurikiranywe cane mu Bushinwa, aho hari amategeko akomeye agenzura ivyo kuvyara ku rugero n’uburenganzira ku bijanye n’irondoka
 Muri videwo yacishijwe ku rubuga hwaniro WeChat, Xu avuga ko adashobora kubireka  "ngo birangire uku nyene”
 Ati: "Ntidushobora kuvuga ko dutsinzwe mu rugamba rwo guharanira uburenganzira bw’abagore bibana, ariko hashobora kuba inzitizi ntoya y’igihe gito”
 Mu 2019 Xu yavuze ko ikibano camuteye igitsure kimusaba ko yovyara umwana hakwishinga akazi kiwe
 Afatiye ku gihe yitura ibi bitaro, avuga ati: "Naje hano nshaka kwitura abahinga kugira bamfashe, ariko nahuye ahubwo n’umuntu yansaba gushira ku ruhande akazi kanje kugira ngo mbanze mvyare umwana”
 "Nahuye n’ibibazo nk’ibi nyene n’abantu bantera igitsure mu kibano, muri ino mico”

Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky  wa Ukraine yagiriza Uburusiya “ubugome” inyuma y’igitero ca misire ku kivuko ca Odesa
 Amasezerano yari gutuma intete za Ukraine zishorwa hanze – yari yateweko igikumu amasaha make imbere y’iki gitero – ubu yahagaze
 Moscou ntaco iravuga kuri iki gitero mu gihe Kyiv ivuga ko imyiteguro ibandanya kugira ngo isubire ishore hanze intete zayo n’aho vyagenze uko
 Ariko ejo ku wa gatandatu, Perezida Zelensky yavuze ko vyerekana ingene Moscou idashobora kwizerwa ko ishobora kwubahiriza aya masezerano
 Avuga ko azokora uko ashoboye kwose gushika aronke ibirwanisho vyo gukingira ikirere bishobora kumanura ibisasu vya misire muri kazoza
 Ukraine ni igihugu kiri mu vya mbere bishora intete hanze, ariko kubera iyi ntambara, amatoni yababa imiriyoni 20 y’intete aracugaraniwe mu bivuko, akaba adashobora gusohoka kubera ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Ibi vyatumye haba ubukene bw’imfungurwa ibiciro na vyo biraduka muri Afrika isanzwe izeye Ukraine n’Uburusiya ku ntete z’ingano
 Mu masezerano yo ku wa gatanu, Uburusiya bwemeye ko butazotera ibivuko bibitswemwo intete zishorwa hanze
 Ariko, amasaha makeya gusa inyuma yo gutera igikumu kuri ano masezerano, ibisasu bibiri vya misire zo mu bwoko bwa Kalibr vyatewe ku kivuko ca Odesa, nk’uko bivugwa n’ibiro vya gisirikare mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine
 Ibindi bisasu bibiri vya misire vyarakorowe n’igisata kijejwe gukingira ikirere, nk’uko ibi biro bibimenyesha
 Ibi biro bimenyesha ko iki gitero ataco cononye kuri ico kivuko
 Iki gitero cariyamirijwe cane
 Umunyamabanga ajejwe imigenderanire wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Antony Blinken yagirije Uburusiya ko buriko butuma ikibazo c’imfungurwa kw’isi cunyuka, anavuga ko iki gitero “gitera amadidane akomeye” ku cizere c’uko uburusiya bushobora gukurikiza aya masezerano
 Ejo ku wa gatandatu yavuze ati: "Uburusiya butegerezwa guhagarika aka gasotoro kandi bushire mu ngiro amasezerano yerekeye intete za Ukraine yateweko igikumu”
 Kremlin gushika ubu ntaco irashikiriza ku mugaragaro ku vyerekeye iki gitero, ariko reta ya Turukiya, ari nayo yatumye aya masezerano ashikwako, ivuga ko abategetsi b’Uburusiya bahakana uruhara rwabo
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi Hulusai Akar  avuga ati: "Tuvuganye n’Uburusiya, Abarusiya batubwiye ko ivy’ico gitero ata kintu na kimwe bakiziko kandi ko bariko barihweza neza iki kibazo”
 Mu yandi makuru, umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Hongrie, Viktor Orban , yavuze ko Ukraine idashobora gutsinda Uburusiya
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu nama ihuza ibihugu bigendera ku mico ya kera, yavuze ko ikintu conyene gishobora kurangiza iyi ntambara ari ibiganiro hagati ya  Washington na Moscow
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Orban, asanzwe adahuza n’abandi bategetsi b’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya kuri iyi ntambara, avuga ati: "Hakenewe iyindi nzira ishobora gushira imbere ibiganiro hakugerageza gutsinda iyi ntambara”
 Umushikiranganji w’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya ajejwe imigenderanire Josep Borrell avuga ko iki gitero ku kivuko ca Odesa cerekana ingene Uburusiya busuzugura amategeko mpuzamakungu
 "Gutera ikibanza gikomeye gicishwako intete zishorwa hanze umusi umwe inyuma y’aho aya masezerano atereweko igikumu muri Istanbul ni ibintu bidashobora kwihanganirwa”, niko yanditse kuri Twitter, akongera y’uko Ubumwe bwa Bulaya “bwiyamirije bwivuye inyuma” iki gitero
 Eka n’umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU Antonio Guterres ariyamiriza yivuye inyuma iki gitero, akavuga ko gushira mu ngiro aya masezerano yerekeye intete za Ukraine ari ngombwa ko ashirwa m,u ngiro

Reta y’Uburundi ikwiye kuva mu majambo ikaja mu bikorwa kugira ngo ishobore kwikura mu kabaregwa ko kwitwa igihugu gikenye kurusha ibindi kw’isi, niko Faustin Ndikumana, umukuru w’ishirahamwe PARCEM, ahanura
 Ibanki y’isi yose iheruka gusohora icegeranyo c’umwaka wa 2021 ku butunzi n’imibereho y’abanyagihugu gishira Uburundi mu kibanza c’inyuma, ivyatumye benshi bongera kwihweza kw’iterambere ry’Uburundi
 Mu kiganiro na BBC, Ndikumana avuga ko imwe mu ngorane nyamukuru Uburundi bufise ari igiturire, akavuga ko mbere ‘ivyo kukirwanya biriko birasubira inyuma ugereranije n’uko vyari bimeze kera’
 Mu gihe umukuru w’igihugu Evariste Ndayishimiye yiyemeje kurwanya igiturire, Ndikumana abona ko ubutungane kuri we ari inzitizi ikomeye
 Ati: “Agerageza gute kukirwanya mu gihe ubutungane butariko burakora
 Ugushaka ndavyumva, mugabo ubutungane butariko burakora, ntashobora kuvuga ngo uriko urarwanya igiturire”
 Umukuru w’iri shirahamwe ryishinze gukangurira Abarundi guhindura ingendo abona ko Uburundi budashobora guterimbere mu gihe hakiri ibihushane iyo hageze gushira mu ngiro imigambi y’iterambere
 Iki cegeranyo c’ibanki y’isi yose ku mwimbu rusangi mu gihugu (Produit National Brut, PIB) ku muntu mu 2021, cerekana ko Uburundi buza mu kibanza ca 195 kuri 196 aho Umurundi umwe aronka USD 240 gusa ku mwaka wose
 Ndikumana avuga ko bapima ibi bisunze “umwimbu wimburwa mu gihugu kanaka kuko niwo uba werekana ubutunzi igihugu kiba gifise, hanyuma bagaca baraba abanyagihugu ingene bangana, umwimbu cimbura mu bisata bitandukanye ugaca ugabanganywa ku banyagihugu bakibamwo, baca baraba rero ico umunyegihugu umwe umwe wese yoba aronka”
 “Ni nk’uko wofata urugo kanaka rurimwo umugore n’umugabo n’abana icenda nk’akarorero, ugaharura ivyo bimbura ku kwezi, amahera baronka ku kwezi, ugaca uyagabura rero na cumi na rimwe, ari ho rero uca ubona amahera umuntu umwe umwe muri urwo rugo ashobora kuronka ku kwezi”
 “Urumva n’ingo zirasumbana, hariho ingo zimbura vyinshi
 Amahera yinjira ari menshi
 Uko muza kuyagabura muri bake, niko ukubaho neza guca kwiyongera
 Iyo muyagabura muri benshi nayo ari make, ubukene buca bwiyongera”
 Ku ruhande rw’Uburundi, Faustin Ndikumana abona ko Uburundi bwimbura bike ariko bugategerezwa kugaburira abantu benshi, bigatuma bwama buboneka ko bukenye
 Uburundi ni igihugu kibeshejweho ahanini n’uburimyi, ibiharuro bikerekana ko 90% ari bo babeshejweho n’isuka
 Icegeranyo c’ikigo ISTEEBU kijejwe kwegeranya ibiharuro giherutse gusohora icegeranyo co mu mwaka wa 2019-2020 cerekana ko abarundi 40% bashobora kumara umusi wose badafunguye
 Ibi biri uku mu gihe abarongoye igihugu bavuga ko umwimbu ari wose
 Mu gihe yariko ashikiriza abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka ivyaranguwe n’ubushikiranganji butandukanye mu gice ca kabiri c’umwaka uheze hari mu kw’icumi kw’umwaka uheze nyene ari nawo iki cegeranyo cerekeye,  umushikiranganji wa mbere Alain-Guillaume Bunyoni  yavuze ko muri ico gihe honyene igihugu cari gifise amatoni menshi y’umusesekara ku mwibu w’ibigori
 Ndikumana abona ko reta n’abakora ivyegeranyo nk’ibi badahuza kubera reta yoyo ikunda gukoresha imvugo ya poritike
 Ati: “Wewe uri mu mabanga, bavuze uko ibintu bimeze birashobora kutakunezera kuko bica vyerekana ko umengo utariko uratunganya ibintu neza
 “Imvugo ya poritike sico kimwe n’iy’abahinga, ni naco gituma turiko turasubirira n’inyuma, umunyeporitike wewe yivugira poritike aho kuraba ivyo abahinga bavuga”
 Mu gusigura ingorane Uburundi bufise zituma bwama buri inyuma mu butunzi, Faustin Ndikumana afatira ku gitabo ishirahamwe ryiwe riherutse gusohora, aho ryihweza imyaka 60 Uburundi bumaze bwikukiye, n’imyaka ibiri y’ubutegetsi bwa Evariste Ndayishimiye
 Muri iki gitabo, yerekana ko imigambi itegurwa ariko ko, iyo hageze kuyishira mu ngiro, “umengo hariko hakorwa ibihushane n’ivyategerezwa kuba biriko birakorwa kugira dushikire intumbero y’iterambere”
 Asigura bimwe muri ibi bihushane biri muri iki gitabo, ica mbere ciyongera ku giturire avuga ko “tugomba guterimbere mu gihe tuvuga ko Uburundi bwikwiye kandi ivyegeranyo vyerekana ko ari ubwanyuma k’isi mu bihugu bitunze”
 Ati: “Uwuja gukira indwara arayirata, none wewe nimba urwaye indwara, ntiwemere ko uyirwaye, wumva uzoyikira gute? Banza wemere ko ukenye”
 Imvo ya kabiri ashikiriza abona ko igihugu kigomba  gutera imbere mu gihe atanzira irashe yo kugiteza imbere ihari ifatiye ku citegererezo c'uko ahandi bigenda
 Ati: “Turagenda tukandika ibitabo, ngo plan national de developpement, tukandika, tugakora amanama, ngo dushaka gufata intumbero mugabo izo recommendations tugaca tubika
 “Gushika ubu nta kintu na kimwe ca programme-vision usanga reta iriko irakorerako”
 Ariko rero, hano ntabona ibintu kumwe na reta ufatiye ku vyo umushikiranganji wa mbere Bunyoni yabwiye abashingamateka n’abakenguzamateka mu kw’icumi kw’umwaka uheze, ari nawo urabwa n’uru rutonde rw’Ibanki y’isi yose, aho yemeza ko integuro ya reta y’igice ca kabiri yakozwe neza mbere hisunzwe uburyo buvuye hagati mu gihugu, akavuga ko ari na ko vyagenze mu gice ca mbere
 Yavuze kandi ko n’ibikorwa bishika 290 vyaranguwe neza hisunzwe integuro ya reta kandi ku rugero rwa 79% ku bushikiranganji bwayiranguye ku rugero ruto, be no kuri 97% ku bushikiranganji bwavyitwayemwo neza gusumba ubundi
  Yemeza ko muri rusangi imigambi reta yari ifise yashizwe mu ngiro ku rugero rwa 88%, mu gihe mu gice ca mbere yaranguwe ku rugero rwa 81%
 Hagati aho, umushikiranganji wa mbere Bunyoni yaremeje ko ubutunzi bw’igihugu muri ico gice bwagabanutse kubera ikiza karanda ca Covid-19, mbere ko hari n’ibindi bikorwa vyari bitegekanijwe bitashoboye kuranguka
 Imvo ya gatatu atanga, avuga ko Uburundi budashobora gutera imbere mu gihe gutanga akazi hatisungwa ubushobozi n’ubumenyi
 Ati: “Wewe uvuga ko ushaka gutera imbere gute udashira imbere incabwenge, abashoboye akazi, ubushakashatsi ngo ubushire imbere, mu nzego nyinshi ugasanga abantu bariko bahabwa amabanga badakurikiza ubushobozi, mu gihe ubu ata n’ibigo vy’ubushakashatsi bihari


none wotera imbere gute”? Ikindi gihushane yerekana, ni uko igihugu kigomba gutera imbere “mu gihe ata buryo buhari bwo kuzana amafaranga mvamakungu mu gihugu kugira afashe mukuzibira ikinogo c’amafaranga Uburundi budafise kandi yongere afashe mw’iboneka ry’amafaranga y’agaciro”
 Ati: “Mbega iryo terambere uzorironka gute? Uzokoresha amarundi? N’aho worara urayafyatura, ukayarwiza muri BRB ntaco azokumarira”
 PARCEM ibona ko amasoko yashobora gutuma igihugu kironka aya mafaranga asa n’ayadakora neza
 Ati: “


 raba n’ikawa yasubiye inyuma, icayi casubiye inyuma, igisata c’ubukerarungendo ntitugiteza imbere kugira ngo bazane amadevises, raba n’amafaranga y’agaciro yovuye mu nzahabu n’ubutare urabona ko vyanse 


none ushaka gutera imbere gute?” “Nta barwizatunga bazana imitahe mu gihugu; kwaka ingurane ntibikunda kuko usanga badashobora kwizera inzego, badashobora kuzizera ku buryo boziha ingurane y’amafaranga aboneka”
 Ikindi gihushane PARCEM ibona gihagaze kw’ikoreshwa ry’amafaranga ya reta ibona ko harimwo igipfungu
 Ati: “Wewe woza gutera imbere gute mu gihe n’ingene reta ikoresha amafaranga ata muco urimwo, umengo amafaranga akoreshwa mu kanywababo, amafaranga adakurikiza imigambi y’iterambere izwi, amafaranga atwarirwa mu gifuri, za cour des comptes zitayakontorora?”
 Mu mwaka uheze wa 2021, Prezida Ndayishimiye yumvikanye anegura bikomeye abo mu nzego zitandukanye n'abamufasha imirimo y'igihugu abagiriza  kuba aribo batuma ibintu bitagenda neza mu gihugu
 Ni mu gihe yaheruka “kuririra imbere” y’abacamanza kw'izina ry'abenegihugu, aho yavuga ko batakironka ubutungane bubereye kubera abo bacamanza bamunzwe n'ibiturire
 Umukuru w’iri shirahamwe rihamagarira abantu guhindura ingendo abona ko umukuru w'igihugu afise utwigoro kandi ko n’amajambo ashikiriza atanga icizere, ariko ko abari musi yiwe batamufasha

Ibibombe vyanyiganyije ikivuko gikomeye ca Ukraine inyuma y’umusi umwe gusa Kyiv na Moscou bashitse ku masezerano yotumye intete za Ukraine zisubira gushorwa hanze
 Ibisasu bibiri vya misire vyatewe mu gisagara ca Odesa gifise ikivuko mu masaha yo mu gaturuturu ko kuri uno wa gatandatu, nk’uko igisirikare ca Ukraine kibimenyesha
 Nk’uko biri muri ano masezerano yaraye ashitsweko, Uburusiya bwemeye kudatera ibivuko bizoba bifise intete ziriko zishorwa hanze
 Ishirahamwe ONU  rivuga ko ano masezerano ari “ikimenyetso c’umwizero” inyuma y’intambara imaze amezi
 Mu butumwa bwacishijwe ku mbuga hwaniro, ibiro vya gisirikare mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine bivuga ko ibisasu bibiri vya misire zo mu bwoko bwa Kalibr vyaguye kuri iki kivuko, mu gihe ibindi bibiri navyo vyakorowe n’igisata kirwanira mu kirere
 Oleksiy Honcharenko, umushingamateka w’akarere, yanditse kuri Telegram ko iki gitero catumye haduka umuriro mu kivuko c’iki gisagara
 "Iyi mihimbiri itera igikumu ku masezerano n’ukuboko kumwe mu gihe ukundi nako gutera misire”, niko Honcharenko yanditse
 "Nico gituma dukeneye indege kugira ngo dusenyure amato y’intambara yose y’Uburusiya ari mu Nyanja yirabura
 Iyi ni yo nzira yonyene yo gushobora gushora hanze intete”
 Ntibiramenyekana neza nimba hari abapfuye n’abakomeretse, canke nimba hari ibintu vyononekaye
 Ejo ku wa gatanu, abategetsi ba Kyiv na Moscou barateye igikumu ku masezerano yotumye imiriyoni n’imiriyoni z’amatoni y’intete zugaraniwe muri Ukraine zishobora gushorwa hanze
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’abaserukizi b’ibihugu, bimwe mu vyo bemeranije ni uko Uburusiya budatera ibivuko mu gihe bizoba biriko birasohora ibidandazwa hanyuma Ukraine nayo ikaba yemeye guherekeza imizigo mu mazi yuzuye ama mines
 Aya masezerano – akaba yafashe amezi abiri kugira ashikweko – yiteze kubandanya mu kiringo c’imisi 120, akazoba ahagarariwe kandi akurikiranirwa hagufi n’ibiro bizoshingwa i Istanbul muri Turukiya, bikazoreramwo abategetsi ba ONU, Turukiya, Ukraine n’ab’Uburusiya
 Arashobora kwongerezwa ikiringo mu gihe impande zompi zovyumvikanako
 Andriy Yermak, umukuru w’ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu Volodymyr Zelensky, ariyamiriza iki gitero akagiriza Uburusiya ko “bubandanya buteza ikibazo c’imfungurwa”
 Umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bwa Ukraine bujejwe imigenderanire, Oleh Nikolenko yongeyeko ati: "Iyi misire y’Uburusiya ni amate Vladimir Putin aciriye ku munyamabanga mukuru w’ishirahamwe ONU, António Guterres no kuri Perezida Recep Erdogan wa Turukiya, bitanze uko bashoboye kwose habe aya masezerano, mbere Ukraine ikaba ibashimira cane”
 Iki gitero kibaye mu gihe abategetsi bo mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Ubwongereza bavuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya mu ntara ya Kherson zishobora kubura ingene zironswa ivya nkenerwa kubera amayira ashobora gukatwa n’ingabo za Ukraine
 Kyiv yaratanguje igitero gikomeye co kwivuna mu bumanuko bw’igihugu, kandi ingabo zayo zarakoresheje inkoho zirasa kure ibisasu vya misire zatanzwe na Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika  mu gutera ikiraro ca Antonovsky i Kherson
 Mu gihe iki kiraro cobomorwa, Uburusiya ntibwokworoherwa gushikira ingabo zabwo

Na Charlotte Attwood, Ko Ko Aung hamwe na Rebecca Henschke\nBBC World Service Abasirikare ba Myanmar (canke Birmanie) baremera ko bakoreye abasivire amahano atagira izina harimwo ubwicanyi, iyicarubozo n’ugusambanya ku nguvu, nk’uko babibwiye BBC mu kiganiro bagiriraniye nayo
 Ku ncuro ya mbere, basiguye ingene bahonyanze agateka ka zina muntu mu gihugu cose bavuga ko ari amategeko bari bahawe
 Uragaba: iyi nkuru irimwo amajambo ashobora gutera ubwoba ajanye n’iyicarubozo no gusambanya ku nguvu  "Bantegetse kukora iyicarubozo, kunyaga no kwica inzirakarengane”
 Maung Oo avuga ko yibaza y’uko yinjijwe mu gisirikare kugira ngo akingire umutekano w’igihugu
 Ariko yisanzwe muri batayo (bataillon) yishe abasivire bari binyegeje mu kigo c’abihebeye Imana mu kwa gatanu 2022
 Avuga ati: "Twategetswe kwegeranya abagabo bose no kubarasa tukabica
 Icababaje cane gusumba ibindi ni uko twategerezwa kwica abatama n’abagore”
 Intahe itangwa n’abasirikare batandatu, harimwo umukaporari, hamwe na bamwe mu babikorewe irerekana amakuru adasanzwe y’ingene igisirikare cakoze amahano um ntumbero yo kugumana ubutegetsi
 Amazina yose ya Myanmar ari muri ino nkuru yarahinduwe mu ntumbero yo gukingira umutekano wabo
 Aba basirikare baherutse gutoroka bakingiwe n’umurwi w’abirwanako uzwi nka People's Defence Force (PDF), umurwi w’abasivire bitwara gisirikare uriko urwana mu ntumbero yo kugarukana demokarasi
 Igisirikare cafashe ubutegetsi gitembagaje reta yari yatowe irongowe na Aung San Suu Kyi mu mwaka uheze
 Ubu kiriko kigerageza guhasha umugumuko w’abasivire bitwaje ibirwanisho
 Ku wa 20 z’ukwa cumi na kabiri umwaka uheze, kajugujugu zitatu zarakikuje ikigwati ca Yae Myet kiri hagati muri Myanmar, gikoragura abasirikare bari bahawe itegeko ryo guca bugurura umuriro
 Abantu n’imiburiburi batanu batandukanye, bavuga ku giti cabo ata n’umwe yavuganye n’uwundi, babwiye BBC ivyabaye
 Bavuga ko abasirikare binjiye  biciyemwo imirwi itatu itandukanye, barasa abagabo, abagore n’abana ata gucagura
 Ari ahantu hinyegeje mw’ishamba riri mu mitumba ya kure muri  Myanmar , Kaporari Aung avuga ati: "Twari dufise itegeko ryo kurasa ikintu ico ari co cose tubonye”
 Avuga ko bamwe mu banyagihugu binyegeza aho bibaza ko bashobora kudashikirwa, ariko ingabo zarahashitse “baca batangura kwiruka bahunga duca turabarasa”
 Kaporari Aung yemeza ko umurwi wiwe wishe wongera uhamba abagabo batanu
 Ati: "Twari dufise kandi itegeko ryo guturira inzu iyo ayi yo yose nini kandi nziza mu kigwati”
 Abasirikare bazungurutse ikigwati cose baturira amazu, bavuza induru ngo “Turira!Turira!” Kaporari Aung yaturiye inzu zine
 Abavuganye na BBC bavuga ko inzu hafi 60 zaturiwe, basiga ikigwati cose ari umunyota
 Ababa muri iki kigwati hfi bose barahunze, ariko si bose
 Hari umuhana umwe wari hagati muri ico kigwati ata bantu bawubamwo
 Thiha avuga ko hari haheze amezi atanu yinjiye mu gisirikare imbere y’uko iki gitero gitangura
 Nk’uko vyari bimeze ku bandi, yari yinjijwe mu gisirikare avuye mu banyagihugu bandi basanzwe kandi ko ata nyigisho za gisirikare yari yahawe
 Aba barikiri (recrues/recruits) bazwi iwabo kw’izina rya Anghar-Sit-Thar canke "abasirikare bahawe akazi "
 Ico gihe yahembwa umushahara mwiza w’amafaranga y’ama Khat ya Myanmar angana na 200,000 ( hafi amadorari y’abanyamerika 100) ku kwezi
 Aribuka ivyabereye kuri ino nzu neza
 Uyu musirikare ati: "Sinshobora kwibagira ingene yakoma akaruru yitakambira, nguma ndavyumva mu matwi yanje kandi n’umutima wanje uguma uvyibuka”
 Abwiye uwari amurongoye, yishuye ati "Nakubwiye kwica umuntu uwo ari we wese tubona "
 Thiha yaciye arasa amasasu y’umuriro muri ico cumba
 Kaporari Aung na we nyene niho yari ari, yumva ingene uyo mwana arira akoma induru ariko arasha abona
 Ati: "Vyari ibintu biteye intuntu
 Twamaze iminota hafi cumi n’itanu twumva arira atabaza mu gihe inzu yariko irasha”
 BBC yararondeye umuryango w’uyu mwana w’umukobwa, ivugana nawo imbere y’ibisigarira vy’inzu yabo
 Incuti yiwe U Myint avuga ko uyu mwigeme yari afise ikibazo co mu mutwe, abavyeyi biwe bakaba bari bamusize muhira bagiye gukora
 Avuga ati: "Yaragerageje gutoroka ariko baramuzibiye barareka arasha abona aratokombera”
 Si we mukobwa wenyene yaboneye amahano mu minwe y’abasirikare
 Thiha avuga ko yari yinjiye mu gisirikare arondera amahera ariko yababajwe n’ivyo yategetswe gukora hamwe n’amabi yiboneye
 Avuga ku murwi w’abakobwa bahagaritse ahitwa Yae Myet
 Intwazangabo yabashikirije ingabo ziwe azibwira ati: "Kora ivyo mushaka”, niko avuga
 Avuga ko basambanije aba bakobwa ku nguvu ariko ko wewe atabikoze
 BBC yararondeye babiri muri aba bakobwa
 Pa Pa na Khin Htwe bavuga ko bahuye n’aba basoda mw’ibarabara maze bagerageza guhunga
 Ntibari ababo mu kigwati ca Yae Myet, bari bahaje baje kuraba umushonyi w’impuzu yahakorera
 N’aho bagerageje kwisigura bakavuga ko atari abarwanyi b’umuhari PDF kandi ko mbere atari ab’aho hantu, baruhiye gupfungirwa mu nyubakwa z’ishure ry’aho hantu, bakaba bahamaze amajoro atatu
 Buri ijoro, basambanywa ku nguvu urutavanako n’abo basirikare bari babafashe, nk’uko babivuga
 Pa Pa ati: "Bampfunze igitambara mu maso baca bampenurira hasi
 Nagumye nkoma induru bariko bansambanya ku nguvu”
 Yaringinze abasirikare ko bomureka ariko bagumye bamukubita mu mutwe mbere bamushirako n’umunwa w’inkoho kugira bamutere ubwoba ko bashobora kumwica
 Asusumira mu kuvuga, mwenewabo Khin Htwe avuga ati:  "Vyabaye ngombwa ko tuvyemera ata mpari kuko twatinya ko bashobora kutwica
 Aba bakobwa bari bafise ubwoba bwo guhura n’aba babakoreye aya mahano ariko bavuga ko bibuka ko bahuye nabo, bamwe bambaye impuzu zisanzwe abandi nabo bari mu mwambaro wa gisirikare
 Mu vyo yibuka, Thiha avuga ati: "Iyo bafashe abakobwa, bavuga bati, ‘ibi bikubayeko kubera ushigikiye PDF’ mu gihe baba bariko barasambanya aba bakobwa”
 Abantu n’imiburiburi cumi nibo bishwe mu kaguma ka Yae Myet, nayo abakobwa umunani bakaba bavugwa ko bamaze imisi itatu yose basambanywa ku nguvu
 Ubwicanyi bw’agahomerabunwa umusirikare Maung Oo yagizemwo uruhara bwabaye ku wa 02 z’ukwa gatanu 2022 mu kigwati citwa Ohake pho, naco nyene kiri mu karere ka Sagaing
 Ivyo avuga ko vyakozwe n’umurwi wa 33 (Light Infantry Division 33) aho bafashe abantu bakabegeraniriza mu rusengero bakabarasa, bisa n’ibivugwa n’ivyabona hamwe n’ibiri mw’ireresi iteye akoba BBC yahawe haciye akanya gato iki gitero kibaye
 Iyi reresi yerekana ibiziga icenda bitondetswe harimwo umugore n’umugabo afise imishatsi isa n’ivu biryamitswe hamwe
 Bose bari bakenyeye igikwembwe kizwi nka sarong, be n’udupira
 Muri iyi videwo harimwo ibimenyetso vyerekana ko barashwe ubw’inyuma kandi ko ababarashe bari babegereye cane
 Twavuganye kandi n’abanyagihugu baba kuri uwo mutumba biboneye aya mabi
 Barashoboye kumenya uyo mugore yari aryamye hampande y’uwo mutama muri iyo videwo
 Yitwa Ma Moe Moe, akaba yari ahetse umwana wiwe afise n’agasakoshi karimwo utuntu dukozwe mu nzahabu
 Yaritakambiye asaba aba basirikare ko batomwaka ibintu vyiwe
 Hla Hla  yari aho hantu ariko bakamureka, avuga ati: "N’aho yari afise uyu mwana, baramusahuye ivyo bintu vyiwe baca baramurasa arapfa
 Baciye batondeka kandi abagabo bagenda bica umwe umwe”
 Uyu mwana yararokotse ubu akaba arezwe n’incuti
 Uyu mupfasoni Hla Hla avuga ko yumvise aba basirikare bigamba kuri terefone ko bishe abantu umunani canke cumi, ko vyari “biryoshe” kwica abantu kandi bavuga ko wari wo “musi wabo wa mbere wari ugenze neza cane”
 Avuga ko bavuye muri ico kigwati baririmba ngo "Turatsinze! Turatsinze!” Uwundi mugore wewe yabonye ingene umugabo wiwe yishwe
 Ati: “Bamurashe mw’itako, hanyuma bamutegeka kwubika inda bamurasa ku gisusu
 Mu nyuma bagiye kumurasa mu mutwe”
 Ashimangira ko atari mu muhari PDF
 "Ni ukuri yari umukozi yakora mu bigazi, niko kazi kari kamubeshejeho
 Mfise umuhungu n’umukobwa kandi simbona ingene ngiye kubandanya mbaho”
 Maung Oo avuga ko yigaya ku vyo yakoze
 Ati: "Rero, ndakubwira vyose
 Ndashaka ko abandi bose babimenya kugira ngo birinde kubona nk’ayo twabonye”
 Aba basirikare bose batandatu bavuganye na BBC baremera ko baturiye amazu n’ibigwati bagasasika hagati muri Myanmar
 Ibi bisigura ko ari ibintu vyari vyateguwe kugira ngo batuze umuntu uwo ari we wese yari ashigikiye abarwanyi
 Ibi bibaye mu gihe bamwe bavuga ko igisirikare kitorohewe muri ino ntambara yo hagati mu gihugu irwanirwa ku mpande zose
 Myanmar Witness – umurwi w’abashakashatsi bakora amatohoza kw’ihonyangwa ry’agateka ka zina muntu  - uvuga ko hari ivyegeranyo birenga 200 bivuga ku bigwati vyaturiwe nk’uku muri ano mezi cumi arangiye
 Bavuga ko ibitero nk’ibi vyo guturira amazu biriko biriyongera cane, aho mu kwa mbere n’ukwa kabiri uno mwaka habaye ibitero n’imiburiburi 40, bikurikirwa n’ibindi n’imuburiburi 66 mu kwa gatanu n’ukwa kane
 Sibwo bwa mbere igisirikare ca Myanmar gikoreshejeje poritike to guturira bakuzako (politique de la terre brûlée / scorched earth policy)
 Yarakoreshejwe ku banyagihugu bo mu bwoko bw’aba Rohingya mu 2017 mu ntara ya Rakhine
 Uturere turi mu misozi turamaze imyaka mirongo dukorerwa ibintu nk’ibi
 Bamwe mu barwanyi b’amoko atandukanye ubu bariko barafasha kwigisha no guha ibirwanisho PDF muri ino ntambara ya kino gihe yo kurwanya igisirikare
 Ishirahamwe Human Rights Watch rivuga ko kuva mu myaka mirongo, Myanmar  irangwamwo umuco wo kudahana aho igisirikare cemerewe kunyaga no kwica uko gishatse, nk’uko aba basirikare babisigura
 Ni gake haba abakurikiranwa ku mabi avugwa ko akorwa n’igisirikare
 Ariko, igisirikare kiri mu ngorane kubera abasirikare batoroka n’ubwicanyi bukorwa na PDF
 Abababa 10
000 barataye igisirikare n’igisoda kuva mu 2021 igihe ubutegetsi butembagarijwe, nk’uko bivugwa n’ishirahamwe ryitwa People's Embrace ryashinzwe n’abahoze mu gisirikare no mu gipolisi
 Michael Martin  wo mu kigo c’abahinga kizwi nka Centre for Strategic and International Studies, avuga ati: "Igisirikare nticorohewe muri ino ntambara irwanirwa ku mpande zose”
 "Kiri mu ngorane yo gutakaza abantu baco haba mu ntwazangabo canke mu basirikare basanzwe, bakaba bariko bapfa ku bwinshi, hakaba hari ingorane zo kwinjiza bashasha, ingorane z’ibikoresho, ibi bikabonekera ku kungene basa n’abagenda batakaza uturere mu bice bitandukanye vy’igihugu”
 Uturere twa Magway na Sagaing (ari naho habereye ibi vyaha) twahoze ari two igisirikare ca Myanmar caronderamwo abo cinjiza
 Ariko ubu, uwaruka ruhitamwo kwigira mu mirwi y’abarwanyi ba PDF
 Kaporari Aung arerekana neza igituma yatorotse: "Iyo mba nibaza ko igisirikare uburuhiro cotsinze iyi ntambara, simba narahambije abanyagihugu birwanira”
 Avuga ko ata musirikare yohirahira ngo ave ku kirindiro wenyene kuko batinya ko bashobora kwicwa na PDF
 Twaregereye Jenerali Zaw Min Tun, umuvugizi w’igisirikare ca Myanmar, tumubaza ibi birego
 Mw’itangazo yasohoye, arahakana ko igisirikare cica abasivire
 Avuga ko ibi bigwati vyompi bivugwa ko vyatewe vyategerezwa guterwa kandi ko abishwe bose bari “abantu bakora iterabwoba”
 Avuga ko igisirikare kitaturiye ibigwati, ko ahubwo ari abarwanyi ba PDF bakora ibi bitero vyo guturira amazu n’ibigwati
 Biragoye kumenya ingene n’igihe iyi ntambara izorangira ariko bisa n’uko izosiga amamiriyoni y’abasivire bahahamutse
