Kaminuza ya Stellenbosch yirukanye umunyeshure wo mu mwaka wa mbere yari yafashwe amasanamu mu kwezi kwa gatanu ariko arihagarika ku bikoresho vy'umunyeshure w'umwirabure
 Uwo munyeshure w'umuzungu yirukanywe inyuma yo gukekwako icaha c'ivangura mu gihe iyo kaminuza yagira amatohoza kuri ico caha
 Abanyeshure benshi barihereje amabarabara basaba ko uwo munyeshure afatirwa ingingo ruhasha
 Iyo kaminuza yarakoze inama yihweza ikibazo c'inyifato (discipline) kuva kw'itariki 15 z'ukwezi kwa gatanu gushika itariki 23 z'ukwezi kwa gatandatu
 Ku musi wa kane, akanama kajejwe inyifato kasanze uwo munyeshure yagirwa n'icaha co kurenga ku mategeko agenga abanyeshure ajanye n'inyifato
 Mw'itangazo, iyo kaminuza igira iti: "Ivyagaragaye vyatumye akanama kajejwe inyifato gafata ingingo ko ata kindi cokorwa atari kwirukana uwo munyeshure ubwo nyene muri kaminuza
" Uwo munyeshure afise imisi itanu yo kujurira kuri iyo ngingo
 Avuga kuri iyo ngingo yafashwe, icegera c'umukuru w'iyo kaminuza, Prof Deresh Ramjugernath yavuze ko iyo kaminuza yitaye kuri ico kibazo "ku buryo bukomeye cane"
 Yagize ati:"Iyi kaminuza ntiyihanganira ivangura rifatiye ku rukoba, amacakubiri, urwanko n'inyifato iharabika agateka k'uwundi muntu
" Amatohoza y'igipolisi na yo ariko arabandanya

Uwahoze ari umusirikare muri Irlande yahamwe n'icaha co kuba umunywanyi w'umuhari wa Islamic State, IS, yaciriwe igipfungo c'amezi 15
 Lisa Smith w'imyaka 40 yagiriwe n'icaha mu kwezi kwa gatanu co kuba umunywanyi wa IS hagati y'itariki 28 z'ukwezi kwa cumi 2015 n'itariki 1 z'ukwezi kwa cumi na kabiri mu 2019
 Sentare yamuhanaguyeko icaha co gushira amahera mw'iterabwoba mu kurungikira amahera umugabo umwe akoresha mu mugwi w'iterabwoba
 Yaciriwe urubanza muri sentare idasanzwe mpanavyaha iri i Dublin
 Umucamanza, Justice Hunt, yavuze ko ari ibintu bikomeye ku munye Irlande wese no kuwahoze ari mu gisirikare c'ico gihugu kwemera gukorera umugwi w'iterabwo ukorera hanze y'igihugu
 Yavuze ko ata nkeka ko yari azi ico yariko arakora
 Ariko yavuze ko we na sentare bihweje kandi ingene yahora yigenza neza kandi ko yagize n'ingorane muri Syria  aho yanakubaguwe
 Ariko yongeyeko ko ivyo vyavuye ku ngingo yiwe yo kuja muri Syria
 Yavuze ko Smith ashobora kuba yarahenzwe vyoroshe, aca aranemera kuguma muri Syria
 Justice Hunt yavuze ko yemera ko gushika ubu ibintu vyahindutse kandi ko yari umuvyeyi mwiza yitayeho umukobwa wiwe yakunda cane
 Nta mpamvu n'imwe yerekana ko yari kuba intandaro yo kubangamira abantu

Umugore w'umukuru w'igihugu ca Ukraine, Olena Zelenska yavuze ko ingwano yo muri Ukraine yatumye umwana wiwe w'umuhungu w'imyaka icenda yipfuza kuba umusirikare
 Mu kiganiro kuri NBC, Zelenska yavuze ko ubu ikintu gusa umuhungu wiwe ashaka gukora ari "kwiga kugwana n'imbokoboko hamwe no kwiga inkoho"
 Yongeyeko ko yizeye ko ubwana bw'umuhungu wiwe 'azobusubizwa'
 Zelenska umugore wa prezida Volodymyr Zelensky yari mu rugendo muri Amerika, aho yateye akamo ko kuronswa ibindi bigwanisho vyinshi muri Ukraine
 Avuga ku ngaruka intambara y'Uburusiya imaze amezi atanu, imaze kugira ku muhungu wiwe, yagize ati:"Imbere y'intambara, umuhungu wanje yakunda intambo zitandukanye
 Yaravuza piano
 Yariga icongereza
 "Ariko kubera ibitero vy'Uburusiya "nta nkeka yipfuza kuba umusirikare
 Ntibikunda ko ndamugarukana muvyo gukunda intambo n'indimi hamwe no muvyo gufasha
 "Ivyo ni vyo ntegerezwa kugwanira ko umuhungu wanje asubizwa, kandi akanezerwa n'ubuzima bwiwe mu buryo bwose
" Zelenska, afise n'uwundi mwana w'imyaka 18 yitwa Oleksandra n'ingene abana n'abavyeyi bamerewe mu rugendo rwiwe arimwo muri Amerika
 Mw'ijambo ry'iminota 15 yashikirije mu nama nshingamateka ya Amerika kuri uyu wa gatatu, yarerekanye amafoto na video vy'abana b'abanye Ukraine bishwe canke bakomekeye mu ntambara
 Kw'ifoto imwe, hari umwana w'imyaka ine, Liza Dmytriyeva, yiciwe mu gitero c'indege mu gisagara ca Vinnytsia kiri hagati hashira uburengero bw'ico gihugu
 Mw'ijambo ryiwe, yagize ati:"Twipfuza ko buri muvyeyi ashobora kubwira abana biwe, 'Genda kuryama mu mahoro
 Nta bitero vy'indege bizosubira, nta n'ibitero vya misile
' Ibi n'ibintu bigoye kwipfuza?" "Ariko kubwo imana mbi, intambara ntirarangira, iterabwoba rirabandanya
" Asaba ibindi bigwanisho n'uburyo bwo kwikingira ibitero vy'indege, yagize ati:"Ndasaba ibigwanisho
 Ibigwanisho bitagenewe gutera intambara ku butaka bw'uwundi muntu, ariko kugira akingire inzu yiwe, n'uburenganzira bwo kuvyuka muri iyo nzu agihema
" Benshi mu bagize inama nshingamateka barashigikiye cane ubufasha Ukraine muvyo umutekano, bakaba bamaze gutanga ibiciye imiriyaridi 8 z'amadolari
 Muri urwo rugendo rwiwe muri Amerika, Zelenska - aherutse gutangura kurangura amabanga y'igihugu ku mu misi iheze - yarabonanye kandi na prezida Joe Biden, umugore wiwe Jill Biden hamwe n'umunyamabanga wa reta ajejwe imigenderanire Antony Blinken

Reta ya Tchad yafashe ingingo yo kubuza abakobwa bakiri bato kuva mu gihugu badahawe uruhusha n’abavyeyi babo, ingingo yiyamirijwe n’amashirahamwe aharanira agateka k’abagore basaba ko iyi ngingo ifutwa
 Asigura iyi ngingo, umushikiranganji ajejwe umutekano Jenerali Idriss Dokony Adiker avuga ko "hari uruja n’uruza rw’abakobwa bakiri bato” bariko bava mu gihugu “mu ntumbero yo gukoreshwa”
 Iri tangazo ribuza amakompanyi y’indege n’amashirahamwe ajejwe gutwara abantu n’ibintu kwakira abakobwa bashaka kwurira indege
 Urwandiko rwa Jen
 Adiker ntirwerekana imyaka y’abakobwa babuzwa ingendo, canke abategerezwa kubaha impusha
 Ishirahamwe riharanira agateka k’abagore, Ligue Tchadienne pour les Droits de la Femme/Chadian Women's Rights League, rivuga ko iyi ngingo yo kubuza abakobwa gusohoka iteye kubiri n’ubwigenge bw’abakobwa bakiri bato be n’uburenganzira bwa kiremwa muntu
 Kubw’iri shirahamwe, iri tegeko ni ivangura rishingiye ku gitsina kuko abahungu bakiri bato muri Tchad nabo nyene bakorerwa uru rudandaza rwa kiremwamuntu
 Icegeranyo c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu rirwanya ivyaha mpuzabihugu kivuga ko urucuruza rw’abantu muri Tchad rwiyongereye muri ino myaka ya vuba
 Kivuga kandi ko igitigiri c’abanya-Tchad badandaza imibiri yabo mu bihugu bibanyi ciyongereye mu 2021

Intumbero ya gisirikare muri Ukraine ntikiri ubuseruko “bwonyene”, nk’uko umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire w'Uburusiya, Sergei Lavrov, abivuga
 Mu kiganiro n’ibinyamakuru vyo mu Burusiya vyegamiye reta, Lavrov yerekana ko intumbero ya Moscou (umugwa mukuru w'Uburusiya) yahindutse inyuma y’aho Uburengero buhereye Ukraine ibirwanisho birasa kure
 Avuga ko ari ngombwa ko Uburusiya ubu bwigiza kure ingabo za Ukraine kugira ngo umutekano wabwo ube mwiza
 Amajambo yiwe aje inyuma y’aho Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zitangarije ko zigiye guha Ukraine ibindi birwanisho birasa kure
 Ukraine izoronswa ibindi birwanisho vya muzinga bine biteye imbere gusumba vyo mu bwoko bwa Himars kugira ngo ishobore guhagarika ingabo z’Uburusiya, ibi vyo muri ubu bwoko bikazoba bibaye 16 nk’uko kizigenza wa Pentagon (ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bwa Amerika), Lloyd Austin, abivuga
 Hagati aho, umutambukanyi w’umukuru w’igihugu ca Ukraine Olena Zelenska  yaraye ashikirije ijambo inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka ya Amerika, aho asaba ibindi birwanisho vyo gukingira ikirere kugira ngo “bidufashe guhagarika iri terabwoba ku ba nya Ukraine”
 Uburusiya bwateye Ukraine muri Ruhuhuma (2), buvuga ko abakoresha ururimi rw’ikirusiya mu karere ka Donbas kari mu buseruko bwa Ukraine bariko bakorerwa ihonyabwoko, ko rero bari bakeneye kubohozwa
 Inyuma y’amezi atanu, Uburusiya bumaze kwigarurira uturere two mu buseruko n’ubumanuko bw’ico gihugu, ariko bukaba bwarananiwe no gushika ku ntumbero y’ubwa mbere yo kwigarurira umugwa mukuru Kyiv, kuva ico gihe bukaba bwaciye butangura kuvuga ko intumbero nyamukuru kwari ukubohoza Donbas
 Amerika yagiriza Uburusiya ko buriko butegura kwiyegurira uturere tw'ubutaka bwa Ukraine
 Kuva mu kwa kabiri, Uburengero bwagiye buha Ukraine ibirwanisho bikomeye ikoresha mu guhangana n’ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Umushikiranganji Lavrov avuga ko ibi vyatumye Uburusiya bwagura intumbero zabwo
 Mu kiganiro na Margarita Simonyan, umunyamakuru azwi cane ku mboneshakure yo mu Burusiya akaba arongoye n’uruganda rwo kwegeranya amakuru kuri televiziyo RT, Lavrov yavuze ati:  "Ntidushobora kwemerera igice ca Ukraine kigenzurwa na [Perezida wa Ukraine Volodymyr] Zelensky


 ko gitunga ibirwanisho bishobora guteza akaga ku butaka bwacu”
 Avuga ati: "Ubu isi iratandukanye”, aha akaba avuga intara zibiri za Kherson na Zaporizhzhia zo mu bumanuko nk’izindi Uburusiya buriko burarondera kwigarurira
 Ingabo za Moscou ziramaze kwigarurira ibice vy’izi ntara zompi
 Lavrov yaravuze cane cane kuri vya muzinga vyo mu bwoko bwa Himars birasa kure – biherutse gutangwa na Amerika – ari vyo vyafashije Ukraine gutera intambwe kanaka
 Mu misi ibiri ikurikirana ingabo za Ukraine zarakoresheje Himars mu gutera ikiraro ngirakamaro kandi gikomeye co muri Kherson isanzwe yarigaruriwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya, nk’uko amakuru abivuga
 Ikiraro ca Antonivskyi ni kimwe muri bibiri Uburusiya bukoresha kugira ngo bushobore gushika mu turere bwigaruriye mu burengero bw’uruzi Dnipro, harimwo igisagara ca Kherson
 Umushikiranganji w’imgenderanire w’Uburusiya avuga ko ibikorwa vy’Uburengero vyo guha Ukraine ibirwanisho ko ari “ishavu ataco rimaze” kandi ko ari “ugushaka kwunyura ibintu”
 Ariko Austin avuga ko “igitero c’ubugome kandi kidafise ishingiro” Uburusiya bwakoze kuri Ukraine ari co catumye amakungu ahaguruka agafata ingingo
 Umugambi w’Uburusiya wo kwagura intumbero zabwo kandi waravuzwe ku wa kabiri n’umuvugizi w’Inama nkuru y’igihugu ijejwe umutekano John Kirby, aho yavuze ko Uburusiya bwariko burategura imigambi yo kwiyegurira uturere tunini tw’ubutaka bwa Ukraine
 Mu turere Uburusiya burondera kwiyegurira harimwo Kherson, Zaporizhzhia, Donetsk na  Luhansk, nk’uko yabivuze  -  ari na two Lavrov avuga ko turiko turaronderwa n’Uburusiya ubu

Perezida Yoweri Museveni wa Uganda yagiriraniye amasezerano yo gufashanya n’umukuru w’umugambwe utavuga rumwe n’uwuri ku butegetsi akaba mbere yari ahanganye nawe mu matora aheruka, Nobert Mao
 Aya masezerano hagati y’umugambwe uri ku butegetsi National Resistance Movement hamwe n’umugambwe Democratic Party yateweko igikumu nijoro ku wa gatatu inyuma y’umubonano hagati y’aba bategetsi babiri mu biro vy’umukuru w’igihugu, State House, i Entebbe
 Perezida Museveni arakeza abategetsi b’umugambwe Democratic Party kuri iki “kimenyetso ca poritike y’abantu bakuze, babona kure kandi bafise intumbero yo kwubaka”
 Mao arongoye uyu mugambwe utavuga rumwe n’uwuri ku butegetsi kuva mu 2010
 Yarerekanye ubuhinga bwiwe mu kuvuga ijambo kandi nk’umunyaporitike arwanya ubutegetsi buri mu minwe y’akarwi kamwe, ariko umugambwe wiwe umaze imyaka mu ndyane z’amacakubiri watumye utakaza ikibanza mu gihugu
 Imbere y’amatora yo mu 2021, yaratakaje abatari bake mu bo bari bafatanije kurongora uyu mugambwe bahisemwo kwigira mu mugambwe mushasha ico gihe National Unity Platform ukirongowe gushika ubu na Robert Kyagulanyi Ssentamu azwi ku ritazirano nka Bobi Wine
 Abashigikiye Mao babona ko iyi ngingo ari inzira nziza yo gukorana hagati y’iyi migambwe ibiri, ariko abamunegura bobo bazobona ko barenganuwe inyuma yo kumwagiriza ko akorana na Museveni
 Abandi nabo banegura poritike ya Uganda bashobora kubona aya masezerano nk’ayandi mayeri y’umukuru w’igihugu yo guca intege abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi bwiwe
 Imbere y’aho, yari yashoboye guhendahenda abanyaporitike batavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi bwiwe mu kubaha ibibanza muri reta
 Abagisigaye ku ruhande rw’abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi nabo babandanya baburabuzwa mu bikorwa vyabo
 Perezida Museveni yasohoye videwo yerekana ingene yariko atera igikumu kuri ano masezerano n’umugambwe Democratic Party:
Uburusiya bufise umugambi wo kwigarurira ubundi butaka bwa Ukraine bukoresheje “amayeri” nk’ayo bwakoresheje mu kwigarurira akarere ka Crimea/Crimée, nk’uko Amerika ibivuga
 Yisunze amatohoza ya Amerika, umuvugizi w’Inama nkuru y’igihugu ijejwe umutekano John Kirby avuga ko Uburusiya buriko burategura inzira yo kwigarurira ubutaka
 Uturere twa Ukraine tumaze kwigarurirwa dushobora kubamwo amatora ya kamarampaka “y’uruhendo” yo kwegekwa ku Burusiya imbere y’ukwezi kw’icenda, nk’uko abivuga
 Uburusiya bwarigaruriye Crimea buyonkoye kuri Ukraine mu 2014 inyuma ya kamarampaka yabonetse cane ko itari yemewe
 Kirby yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Turashaka kubisigurira neza abanyagihugu ba Amerika
 Nta n’umwe ashobora kwihenda
 [Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya] ariko arakoresha amayeri yo mu 2014"
 Yagiriza Uburusiya gushira intwaro mu minwe y’abategetsi batemewe begamiye ku Burusiya mu burongozi bw’uturere twa Ukraine twigaruriwe, mu ntumbero yo gutegura amatora ya kamarampaka yo kwegukira Uburusiya
 Kirby avuga ko ibizoba muri ano matora bishobora gukoreshwa n’Uburusiya mu “kugerageza gusaba ko ubutaka bwa Ukraine bubwegukira”
 Uburusiya bwaramaze gushiraho abategetsi b’uturere babwo mu bice vya Ukraine bumaze kwigarurira
 Crimea yigaruriwe n’Uburusiya mu 2014 inyuma y’amatora ya kamarampaka yateguwe gihutihuti - amatora amakungu yafashe ko ateye kubiri n’amategeko, aho abatoye bahisemwo kwegukira Uburusiya
 Abenshi mu bari bashigikiye Kyiv baranse kuja muri ayo matora kandi n’imyiyamamazo ntiyabaye mu muco
 Amatora asa n’ayo mu tundi turere twa Ukraine nta nkeka ko ashobora kuba nk’aya nyene, aho uwo ari we wese yorwanya umugambi wo kwegukira Uburusiya yorwanywa bikomeye
 Kirby avuga ko ashize ahabona imigambi y’Uburusiya “kugira ngo isi imenye ko umugambi uvugwa wo kwigarurira ubutaka bwa Ukraine ari ikintu categuwe imbere y’igihe, kandi ko kitemewe n’amategeko”, mbere akaba yavuze ko Amerika n’incuti zayo bizotegerezwa kwihora vuba bwango
 Avuga ko mu turere dushobora kwigarurirwa harimwo Kherson, Zaporizhzhia, Donetsk na Luhansk

Abashingamateka ba Sri Lanka batoye umushikiranganji wa mbere Ranil Wickremesinghe nka prezida mushasha w'ico gihugu, n'aho adakunzwe n'abanyagihugu
 Wickremesinghe ahanganye n'ikibazo co gutwara igihugu  kigeze ahatemba mu butunzi no gusubiza ibintu mu buryo inyuma y'amezi n'amezi y'imyiyerekano y'urutavanako
 Yatsinze bikomeye uwo bari bahanganye mu guhiganirwa ico kibanza, Dullus Alahapperuma, ku majwi 134 kuri 82 mu matora yo mu nama nshingamateka
 Uwahora aramutswa igihugu ca Sri Lanka Gotabaya Rajapaksa yahunze igihugu mu ndwi iheze
 Yahungiye mu mazinga ya Maldives hanyuma aja i Singapour inyuma y'aho abari mu myiyerekano batereye ikirimba ciwe  n'izindi nyubakwa za reta, bamuhamagarira gutanga imihoho
 Banahamagariye kandi umushikiranganji wiwe wa mbere Wickremesinghe, afitaniye ubucuti bukomeye n'umuryango wa  Rajapaksa, yari yagenywe muri ayo mabanga mu kwezi kwa gatanu,  gukinjura
 Abari mu myiyerekano baraturiye inzu yiwe mu ndwi iheze baranagira igitero ku biro vy'ubushikiranganji bwa mbere i Colombo mu kwiyamiriza intwaro yiwe
 Abantu muri Sri Lanka bamaze  amezi n'amezi bari mu myiyerekano kubera igihugu kiri mu bukene butagira izina kikaba gihanganye n'ikibazo c'ibura ry'ibifungurwa, igitoro hamwe n'ibindi bintu vya nkenerwa
 Inyuma yo gutorwa, Wickremesinghe yabwiye inama nshingamateka ko igihugu cari "mu bihe bigoye cane" kandi ko hari " Ibibazo bikomeye vyo gutorera inyishu"
 Uwo mugabo w'imyaka 73 yahamagariye abo batavuga rumwe gukorana na reta yiwe ku neza y'igihugu
 Vyizewe ko itorwa ryiwe rishobora kugarukana ituze muri politike, kugira ico gihugu gisubire mu biganiro n'ikigega c'isi yose FMI (International Monetary Fund) ku mugambi wo kukigoboka
 Nk'umushikiranganji wa mbere, Wickremesinghe yari yagize uruhara muri ivyo biganiro mu kwezi guheze
 Umugambwe uri ku butegetsi muri Sri Lanka, Podujana Peramnua, uvuga ko benshi mu banywanyi bawo bashigikiye Wickremesinghe kubera icizere bamufitiye ku vyerekeye ubutunzi
 Umunyamabanga mukuru w'uwo mugambwe, Sagara Kariyawasam yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru rya Reuters ati: "Twumva ko Ranil Wickremesinghe ari we muntu wenyene afise uburambe, ubumenyi n'ubushobozi bwo gutora inyishu z'ingorane y'ubutunzi
" Uwo mugabo w'umunyamategeko, Wickremesinghe, amaze kuba umushikiranganji wa mbere incuro zitandatu, akaba amaze muri politike ya Sri Lanka imyaka 45
 Ariko benshi mu bari mu myiyerekano ntibamwerekwa - bamubona nk'umwe mu bahoze muri politike y'ico gihugu - hakaba hari ubwoba ko itorwa ryiwe rishobora gutuma haba iyindi migumuko n'imyiyerekano

Abarepubulikani batari bake bashigikiye aba-Democrats mu nama nshingamateka ya Amerika mu kwemeza integuro y’itegeko rishobora kuzokingira abubakanye basangiye ibitsina
 Aba-Democrats babona ko Sentare Nkuru (urukiko rw'ikirenga) ya Amerika ishobora gufuta uburenganzira bw’abubakanye basangiye ibitsina, ariko Abarepubulikani babinegura biyamirije iyi nteguro bafata nk’ugushaka kubahendahenda
 Mu 2015, Sentare Nkuru ya Amerika yaremeje ko abubakana basangiye ibitsina babifitiye uburenganzira mu gihugu cose
 Ariko mu kwezi guheze, yarafuse uburenganzira bwo gukorora inda bwari bumaze igihe kirekire bukingiwe n’ibwirizwashingiro
 Amahirwe y’uko haba itegeko rikingira abubakanye basangiye ibitsina hamwe n’abadasangiye ubwoko (Respect for Marriage Act) asa n’uko ari make mu nama nkenguzamateka ifise ibitigiri bingana hagati y’aba-Democrats n’abarepubulikani
 Abarepubulikani bababa 47 bishize hamwe n’aba-Democrats mu kwemeza iyi ngingo ku majwi 267-157 ejo ku wa kabiri inyuma y’aho abarongoye abarepubulikani bahereye uburenganzira abanywanyi b’umugambwe wabo gutora ikiri ku mutima
 Abarenga bitatu vya bine vy’abashingamateka b’abarepubulikani bariyamirije iyi nteguro kuri iki kibazo kimaze igihe kirekire ari ikigeragezo ca poritike ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku mico ya kera
 Abagendera ku mico ya kera basanzwe banegura iyi nteguro bagabisha ko aya matora ari umutego w’aba-Democrats kugira bagondoze abarepubulikani kwerekana aho bahagaze mu gihe himirije amatora y’abashingamateka yo mu kw’icumi na rimwe uno mwaka
 Umushingamateka Jim Jordan wo muri Ohio avuga ati: "Turi ng’aha mu manyanga ya poritike"
 Uwurongoye inkehwa mu nama nshingamateka Kevin McCarthy hamwe n’uwujejwe indero ku ruhande rw’inkehwa Steve Scalise batoye oya, ariko uwugira gatatu mu bashingamateka b’abarepubulikani Elise Stefanik yatoye ego
 Uwundi kandi yatoye ego ni umurepubulikani azwi cane Liz Cheney yigeze gucanamwo muri kahise n'umugore bavukana wo mu bubukana basangiye ibitsina, igihe Cheney yiyamiriza abubakana basangiye ibitsina
 Iyi nteguro y’itegeko izoshobora kandi gutuma abubakanye badasangiye ubwoko bakingirwa n’amategeko
 Aba-Democrats bazanye iyi nteguro inyuma y’aho ba nyarwinshi bagendera ku mico ya kera bo muri Sentare Nkuru y’igihugu mu kwa gatandatu bahinduriye itegeko rizwi nka Roe v Wade  ryo mu 1973 ryatanga uburenganzira bwo gukorora inda
 Umucamanza ari ku ruhande rw’abagendera ku mico ya kera Clarence Thomas yanditse mu kwezi guheze ko n’ibindi vyemezo vyo muri kahise ku bibazo nk’ivy'abubakana basangiye ibitsina hamwe n’ivyo kugenzura imvyaro bishobora gusubirwamwo
 Ariko umucamanza Samuel Alito, uwundi agendera ku mico ya kera, yarasiguye neza mu ngingo yiwe ko "iki cemezo cerekeye uburenganzira butangwa n’ibwirizwashingiro bwo gukorora inda gusa”
 Abarepubulikani baneguye ibivugwa n’aba-Democrats ko ukwubakana hagati y’abadasangiye ubwoko gushobora kubangamirwa, berekana ko umucamanza Thomas ari umwirabure yarongoye umuzungukazi
 Umukuru w’aba-Democrats mu nama nkenguzamateka Chuck Schumer ejo ku wa kabiri yavuze ati: "Reka duhangane naco: Uku ni ukuzana ca civugo ca 'Kwongera kugira Amerika Igihangange' muri Sentare Nkuru y’igihugu
 Uruhande rw’intagondwa muri Sentare Nkuru y’igihugu rugomba kugarukana iki civugo”
 'Kwongera kugira Amerika Igihangange' (Make America Great Again), ni icivugo cakoreshwa n’uwahoze ari umukuru w’igihugu Donald Trump mu myiyamamazo y’amatora yatsinze mu 2016
 Umushingamateka Schumer ntiyiyemeje gutwara mu nama nkenguzamateka iyi nteguro kugira ije mu matora
 Ivyabaye ejo ku wa kabiri vyerekana intambwe Amerika imaze gushikako kuri kino kibazo c’abubakana basangiye ibitsina cigeze kuba kibacanishamwo cane, neza na neza inyuma y’imyaka 14 Barack Obama, umu-Democrat, yariko yiyamamariza kurongora igihugu, avuze ko ukwubakana ari hagati y’umugabo n’umugore
 Amatohoza yakozwe n’ikigo Gallup mu kwa gatandatu yerekana ko igitigiri c’abashigikiye abubakana basangiye ibitsina ciyongereye, aho 70% vy’Abanyamerika bakuze bashigikiye ubugeni nk’ubwo

Prezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya ari muri Irani kuri uno wa kabiri, mu rugendo rwiwe rugize kabiri hanze kuva atanguye igitero ciwe kuri Ukraine mu kwezi kwa kabiri
 Putin yahuye na Prezida wa Irani, Ebrahim Raisi, agishika i Tehran, akaba kandi yitezwe guhura n’umutegetsi w’ikirenga wa Irani Ayatollah Ali Khamenei n’umukuru w’igihugu ca Turukiya Recep Tayyip Erdogan
 Ibibazo vyo gushora intete hanze, ivya Syria na Ukraine bizoganirwako i Tehran, nk’uko umutegetsi wo muri reta ya Turukiya abivuga
 Ibi bikurikiye ivyagiriji vya Amerika vyo mu ndwi iheze vy'uko Irani igire ironse  Uburusiya indege za drone zishika amajana zo gukoresha mu rugamba muri Ukraine
 Ahejeje kubonana na Bwana Raisi, Bwana Putin yavuze yuko imigenderanire hagati y'Uburusiya na Irani iriko "iratera imbere ku ntambwe nziza"
 Bwana Putin yavuze yuko ibihugu vyombi biriko birakomeza ugukorana mu bisata nk'ivy'umutekano mpuzamakungu, urudandaza no "guheraheza ikibazo ca Syria"
 Umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya akora ingendo mpuzamakungu nke mu bihugu vyahoze bigize ubutegetsi bw’igisoviyeti kuva intambara yadutse muri Ukraine
 Mu kwa gatandatu, Putin yakoze urugendo rwiwe rwa mbere mu makungu kuva mu kwa kabiri igihe agendera ibihugu vya Tajikistan na Turkmenistan, vyompi vyari mu cahoze citwa URSS/USSR ubu bikaba bitwarwa n’ubutegetsi bw’agahotoro kandi bikaba ari incuti z’Uburusiya
 Uru rugendo rwo kuri uno wa kabiri ruza guha akaryo Perezida Putin ko gutsimbataza ubucuti na Irani, igihugu kiri muri bike bigisigaranye imigenderanire na Moscou kandi gisangiye ibihano vy’ubutunzi vyafashwe n’Uburengero
 Uru rugendo ruje inyuma y’ivyavuzwe n’abategetsi ba Amerika mu ndwi iheze ko Tehran yariko itegura guha Uburusiya amajana n’amajana ya za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) bushobora gukoresha mu ntambara yabwo muri Ukraine
 Mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru kuri uyu wa mbere, Yuri Ushakov, umuhanuzi mukuru wa Putin mu vy’imigenderanire, avuga ati: "Umubonano na Khamenei ni kirumara cane
 "Ibiganiro vyizewe vyarateye imbere hagati yabo ku bibazo nyamukuru hagati y’ibihugu vyompi be no ku rwego mpuzamakungu”
 Umwanditsi mukuru wa BBC ku Burusiya Gutera umubanyi wawe, igihugu cikukiye, bitera bigutesha abagenzi
 Uburusiya bumaze gutakaza incuti zitari nke inyuma y’uko buteye Ukraine
 Mu burengero, Moscou yaragizwe igicibwa
 Ariko Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu w’Uburusiya) irashaka cane kwerekana ko ibihano yafatiwe n’amakungu vyananiwe no kwigizayo Uburusiya, igihugu ca mbere kinini kw’isi, kandi ko mbere n’ibihugu bimwe bimwe vy’incuti bikiri kumwe nayo
 Ibi ni nka Turukiya na Irani
 Uburusiya buzokoresha iri koraniro ry’ibihugu bitatu kuri Syria mu kugerageza kwerekana ko bugisigaranye incuti zikomeye kandi ko bugifise ijambo muri politiki y’isi
 Ariko ngaha ntituriko tuvuga ko ibi ari incuti pfa mpfe
 Turukiya na Irani navyo nyene ni abakeba b’Uburusiya
 Turukiya n’Uburusiya bishigikiye impande zishamiranye muri Syria no muri Libya; biriko birahiganira gushinga imizi mu bumanuko bw’akarere ka Caucase; ‘drones’ z’intambara za Turukiya ziriko zirafasha igisirikare ca Ukraine
 Hanyuma kuri Irani nayo, iriko irahiganwa n’Uburusiya kw’isoko mpuzamakungu y’amasoko ntanganguvu
 Ni vyo, Uburusiya, Turukiya, na Irani birafise inyungu rusangi zimwe zimwe
 Ariko ibi ntibisigura ko bifitaniye ubugenzi bw’igihe kirekire
 Turukiya n’Uburusiya vyashigikiye impande zishamiranye mu ntambara ya Syria bikaba biriko birarondera ingene indyane zigabanuka kuva mu mezi aheze
 Ariko iyi nama ije mu gihe Turukiya igabisha ko ishobora gutangura igitero gishasha mu buraruko bwa Syria ku nyeshamba z’aba-kurd zishigikiwe na Amerika, ingingo Irani n’Uburusiya vyompi vyiyamiriza
 Iki gitero kiri mu nteguro za Perezida Erdogan zo gushinga akarere gatekanye k’ibirometero 30 ku rubibe Turukiya ihana na Syria
 Mu ndwi iheze, Inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano yarumvikanye gusubira kurungika imfashanyo mu turere twa Syria turi mu minwe y’inyeshamba mu kiringo c’amezi atandatu
 Uburusiya bwarahagaritse iciyumviro c’uko ico gikorwa cobandanya mu kiringo c’umwaka wose
 Ankara (umugwa mukuru wa Turukiya) yaranse gufatira ibihano Moscou kuva Putin atanguye igitero kuri Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), reta ya Erdogan ikaba irondera kuba umuhuza
 Iyi nama ishobora guha akaryo umukuru w’igihugu ca Turukiya ko kugerageza gushika ku masezerano hagati y’abategetsi b’Uburusiya na Ukraine kugira ngo intete ziharurwa mu matoni imiriyoni 22 zikenewe cane kw’isi zishobore gushorwa hanze
 Mu ndwi iheze, umushikiranganji wa Turukiya ajejwe kwivuna abansi yavuze ko impande zompi zari zumvikanye ku kungene amayira ashobora gucishwamwo amato y’ingano yokingirwa
 Amato y’intambara y’Uburusiya mu Nyanja Yirabura (Mer Noire/Black Sea) avugwa ko azibira ibidandazwa bisohoka canke vyinjira, mbere BBC yashoboye kuronka ivyemezo vyinshi vyerekana ko ingabo za Moscou zivye zigashora hanze ingano za Ukraine
 Ayandi mayira yaratezwemwo amamine menshi
 Ushakov ati: "Ikibazo c’intete za Ukraine kiraganirwako na Erdogan
 Turiteguye kubandanya ibikorwa kuri iki kibazo"
 Ariko ibi biganiro bije mu gihe abategetsi b’akarere be n’abarimyi hafi y’akarere kaberamwo intambara bagiriza Uburusiya ko butera amabombe n’ibigirankana imirima y’ingano
 Oleh Pylypenko, umunyaporitike w’akarere mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine akaba yahoze ari impfungwa y’Uburusiya, yabwiye BBC ko abarimyi mu karere kiwe hafi y’igisagara ca Mykolaiv kiri mu bumanuko bakibandanya baterwa vya muzinga n’ibisasu vya misire vy’urutavanako
 Avuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya "zateye amabombe imirima, amamashini yo kurima hamwe n’ububiko bw’intete”, kandi ko abarimyi benshi “bakozweko ivyo bitero mbere baranakomereka”
 Yongerako y’uko "abajejwe kuzimya imiriro mu gisagara ca Mykolaiv batinya kujayo kubera kwoba ari ukwiroha
 Imiriro myinshi yarazimijwe ku twigoro twacu
 Ariko ubu rero amabombe ariko ariyongera”

