Umwongereza yerekanywe muri videwo atabaza umushikiranganji wa mbere Boris Johnson ko yomufasha, asa n’uwuri mu minwe y’inyeshamba zishaka kwiyonkora zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya mu karere ka Donesk kitangaje ko ari igihugu cigenga, ni mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 John Harding ari mu myaka ya 50 akaba aturuka muri Sunderland aboneka ariko arabazwa n’umunyamakuru w’imboneshakure yo mu Burusiya
 Muri iyo videwo, avuga  y’uko ashobora gucirirwa urubanza rwo gupfa
 Ubushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire bw’Ubwongereza buvuga ko buhagaritswe umutima n’ipfungwa ryiwe
 Bizwi ko Harding yafashwe mpiri mu kwa gatanu igihe abarwanyi ba Ukraine barwanira muri rwa ruganda rw’ivyuma rwa Azovstal bategekwa kwishikana
 Aba barwanyi bari bamaze igihe bwarwanira igisagara ca Mariupol kiri mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine
Iyi videwo ivuga ko yari umwe muri abo barwanyi barwanira i Azov
 Harding yabwiye abagenzi ko yari mu ngabo za Ukraine zijejwe gukingira igihugu (Garde Nationale/ National Guard)
 Abagenzi n’umuryango wa Harding babwiye BBC ko uwo iyi videwo yerekana ari we nyene, kandi ko umuryango wiwe uriko urafashwa n’ubushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire
 Yatanguye kurwanira mu karere ka Donbas kari mu buseruko bwa Ukraine kuva mu 2018
 Yari aherutse kubwira BBC ko yari yagiyeyo kugira akoreshe ubuhinga bwiwe nk’umusirikare w’umuganga, gufasha mu rugamba rwo kurwanya inyeshamba zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya
 Abandi bagabo babiri b’Abongereza, Aiden Aslin na Shaun Pinner, nabo nyene bafatiwe i Mariupol, baramaze gucirirwa urwo gupfa na sentare yegamiye Uburusiya mu citwa Repubulika ya Donesk
 Aba bose hamwe na Harding basa n’abagiriye rimwe muri Ukraine kandi bari bamaze kuba abenegihugu bayo
 Sentare ya Repubulika ya Donesk ntiyemerwa n’amakungu
 Umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire Liz Truss avuga ko ibi bihano vyo gupfa ari “imanza z’amanyanga kandi zitemewe na gato”
 Reta y’Ubwongereza ivuga ko bakwiye gufatwa nk’impfungwa z’intambara hisunzwe amategeko ari mu masezerano ya Genève
 Muri ino ndwi, Paul Urey, umwongereza akora mu gisata c’ubutabazi, yarapfuye ari mu minwe y’inyeshamba zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 Abategetsi ba Donesk bavuga ko yapfiriye mw’ibohero ku wa 10 Mukakaro (7) kubera uburwayi yari afise hamwe “n’akabonge”
 Umuvugizi w’ubushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire, Commonwealth n’iterambere avuga ati: "Turiko turafasha umuryango w’umwongereza kandi turahagaritswe umutima n’ipfungwa ryiwe
