 Mobutu Sese Seko, sekuru wa Malo Ndimba Mobutu, azwi nk’umukuru w’igihugu ca Congo kuva mu 1965 gushika 1997, igihe yirukaniwe ku butegetsi n’inyeshamba z’umuhari AFDL zari zirongowe na Laurent-Désiré Kabila, zifashwe mu mugongo n'ibihugu birimo u Rwanda na Uganda
 Ku butegetsi bwiwe, yahinduye izina ry’iki gihugu citwa Congo Kinshasa, acita Zaïre kuva mu 1971 gushika ubutegetsi bwiwe busenyuwe mu 1997
 Abonwa nk’umukuru w’igihugu yatwaye nabi cane icahoze citwa Zaïre ku buryo kuva avuye ku butegetsi igihugu  gushika ubu kitararonka amahoro
 Filip Reyntjens, umwigisha wa kaminuza akaba n’umuhinga ku karere k’ibiyaga binini vya Afrika, aherutse kubwira BBC ko ibibazo iki gihugu kirimwo ari inkurikizi z’intwaro mbi yiwe, aho avuga ko “kuva mu myaka ya 1970, yagiye arasambura bukebuke iki gihugu kitagishoboye kurangura amabanga shingiro yaco kuva kera cane”
 Yishimikije izina rizwi muri kahise, umwuzukuru wiwe Mobutu Ndimba Malo, avuga ko ari isura nshasha ije kunagura intara ya Nord-Ubangi

