Abasirikare batari musi ya 7200 ba Ukraine barabuzwe irengero kuva igitero c’Uburusiya gitangura, nk’uko umuhuza wa Ukraine (ombudsman/canke umuvunyi mukuru mu kinyarwanda) Oleh Kotenko abivuga
 Abenshi muri bo bari mu minwe y’Uburusiya, nk’uko yabibwiye imboneshakure yo muri Ukraine, Suspilne TV
 Umuhuza Kotenko avuga ko igisirikare ca Ukraine cari catangaje imbere y’aha ko abashika 2000 ari bo bari babuzwe irengero
 Ariko avuga ko muri kino gitigiri kinini harimwo ingabo zijejwe umutekano w’igihugu (Garde Nationale/National Guard), ingabo zijejwe gucungera imbibe, hamwe n’abakozi bo mu gisata c’umutekano
 Kotenko, umukuru w’igisata ca Ukraine kijejwe ababuzwe irengero, avuga ati: "Ikigo cacu kijejwe kwakira abahamagara ku materefone gifise abagera ku 7200”
 Avuga ko yizeye y’uko “bitebe bitebuke” bazoguzwa n’impfungwa z’intambara z’Abarusiya hanyuma bagasubizwa iwabo
 Caba igisirikare ca Ukraine, caba ic’Uburusiya, nta wuragira ico ashikirije ku mugaragaro kuri iki kibazo
 Yaba Kyiv canke Moscou, uruhande rwose ruvuga ko rwafashe mpiri ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’impfungwa z’intambara kuva Uburusiya buteye Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2) uno mwaka
 Impande zompi ziramaze guhanahana impfungwa incuro zitari nke
 Ku wa Mungu, umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi Oleksii Reznikov yatangaje ko Kyiv itegura “umuriyoni w’abasirikare”, bahawe ibirwanisho vya OTAN/NATO kugira bisubize ubumanuko bw’igihugu bwigaruriwe n’Abarusiya
 Ashimangira ko kwisubiza uturere turi mu micungararo y’Inyanja Yirabura (Mer Noire/Black Sea) ari kirumara ku butunzi bw’igihugu
 Hagati aho, amajambo yiwe asa n’ayatera akamo mu kurondera ababashigikira gusumba ko yoba yerekana integuro ifadika, nk’uko abihweza ibinti n’ibindi babibona

Iran itegura guha Uburusiya za ndege zitagira abadereva, zizwi nka drones, zishobora kuba ziharurwa mu majana, mu ntambara yabwo muri Ukraine, zimwe muri zo zikaba zifise ubushobozi bwo gukoreshwa mu ntambara, nk’uko umutegetsi wo muri Amerika abivuga
 Jake Sullivan, umuhanuzi wo mu biro bikuru vy’umukuru w’igihugu, Maison Blanche/White House, mu vyo umutekano w’igihugu, avuga ko amakuru Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yaronse yerekana ko Irani iriko itegura kwigisha ingabo z’Uburusiya gukoresha izi drones
 Avuga kandi ko bitaramenyekana neza nimba Irani yaramaze kuzitanga
 Izi ndege zitagira abadereva zifise uruhara runini mu ntambara ibandanya ku mpande zompi, ni ukuvuga kuri Ukraine n’Uburusiya
 Mu ndwi iheze, Ukraine yasavye imfashanyo y’ibihumbi vya drones kugira ziyifashe mu ntambara yayo
 Sullivan avuga kandi ko amakuru y’itohoza Amerika yaronse ashigikira iciyumviro c’uko igitero c'Uburusiya mu buseruko bwa Ukraine "gitwara uburyo bwinshi mu kubungabunga ibirwanisho vyabwo”
 Avuga kandi ko izi ndege za Irani zitagira abadereva zakoreshejwe imbere y’aha n’inyeshamba z’aba Houthi bo muri Yemen mu gutera Arabie Saoudite/Saudi Arabia
 Amajambo yiwe ashikirijwe imbere y’uko Perezida wa Amerika Joe Biden  agendera Israel na Arabie Saoudite muri ino ndwi
 Nta na kimwe muri ibi bihugu bibiri kirinjira mu bihugu vyafatiye ibihano Uburusiya kubera intambara bwatanguje muri Ukraine
 Israel ibona igihugu ca Irani nk’akaga nyamukuru mu karere, na rirya gisaba ko ifutwa
 Amerika n’incuti zayo bamaze gufashisha Ukraine ibirwanisho bifise agaciro k’imiriyaridi zitari nke z’amadorari y’Abanyamerika kuva igitero gitanguye mu kwa kabiri
 Sullivan avuga ko Amerika izobandanya “ishigikira cane igisata co kwivuna abansi ca Ukraine”

Peres Jepchirchir  yatahukanye ihiganwa rya Olempike mu kwiruka marathon ku ruhande rw’abagore, hamwe na Francine Niyonsaba ntibazoja mw’ihiganwa mpuzamakungu ryo kunonora imitsi (World Athletics Championships) muri kuno kwezi
 Uyu munya-Kenya Jepchirchir yarahinyagaye mu mafyigo, na yo umurundikazi Niyonsaba yagize ikibazo mu kuguru
 Jepchirchir yabwiye ikinyamakuru co muri Kenya The Nation ati: "Ndababara mu mafyigo no mu kuguru kwose”
 Niyonsaba, umunonotsi yatahukanye umudari w’ifeza mw’ihiganwa rya Olempike mu gusiganwa ku metero 800 mu 2016, yimuriwe ku ntera za 5000 na 10000
 Uyu murundikazi w’imyaka 29 yabujijwe kwiruka kuri izi ntera 800 yari amenyereye mu 2019 kubera ikibazo c’imisemburo ya testosterone iri ku rugero rwo hejuru
 Jepchirchir w’imyaka 28, yaratahukanye umudari w’inzahabu i Tokyo mu mwaka uheze mu kwiruka ku mwanya w’amasaha abiri n’iminota 27 n’amasegonda 20, atsinda mugenziwe Brigid Kosgei n’umunyamerikakazi Molly Seidel
 Uyu munonotsi yatsindiye amahiganwa mpuzamakungu ya marathon ku ruhande rw’abagore mu 2016 na 2020 yongerako ati: "Ndababaye cane ariko sinohava nunyura imvune na rirya tugifise irindi higanwa mu mwaka uza imbere y’uko nja kurwanira intsinzi yanje ya Olempike mu 2024 mu nkino zizobera i Paris”
 Jepchirchir yatsindiye ihiganwa rya mbere rya marathon i Boston mu kwa kane akaba yaratevye gushirwa ku rutonde rw’umurwi w’abakenyakazi bane ba Kenya bazohiganwa muri marathon i Eugene
 Ku ruhande rwiwe, Niyonsaba avuga ko ata kundi yari kugira atari ukuva muri iri higanwa rizobera muri Amerika
 Aciye ku rubuga rwa Instagram yanditse ati: "Haraciye hafi ukwezi kumwe ntanguye kwumva imvune yo mu kirenge
 Jewe n’abo dufashanya twarakoze ibishobora vyose kugira nkire
 "Ubu meze neza ariko sinashoboye kwimenyereza muri iki kiringo cose, rero uko meze ubu sinumva ko vyonshobokera guhiganwa uko ndavyipfuza”
 Niyonsaba, Umurundikazi wenyene amaze gutsindira umudari wa Olempike, yarakoze birashimwa mw’ihiganwa Diamond League ryabereye i Doha mu kwa gatanu, aho yiruka imetero 3000
 Mu mahiganwa ya Olempike y’umwaka uheze, yahejeje ari mu kibanza ca gatanu ku metero 10000 ku ruhande rw’abagore, akaba yaciye umuhigo, kuko yari ahejeje guhindura intera ahiganwako inyuma yo kubuzwa guhiganwa hagati y’imetero 400 na 1500 kubera imisemburo ya testosterone irenze urugero
 Aya mahiganwa mpuzamakungu yo kwinonora imitsi (World Athletics Championships) azotangura ku wa gatanu akazorangira ku wa 21 Mukakaro (7)

Igihe umurundikazi Esperance Habonimana, umukobwa muto mu bitavye ihiganwa rya Wafcon, yatangura gukina umupira w'amaguru, yatanguye nk'abandi bose muri Africa - akina mu migwi y'abagabo
 Uwo mukobwa muto cane mw'ihiganwa rya Afrika ry'umupira w'amaguru mu bagore (Wafcon) avuga ko impamvu ari imwe gusa isanzwe
 Uwo mukobwa w'imyaka 15 yabwiye BBC Sport Africa ati:"Narakina umupira ariko sinigeze menya ko hariho imigwi  y'umupira w'amaguru y'abagore
" "Nakina mu migwi y'abagabo na basaza banje kubera mu mutwe wanje sinigera nibaza ko hariho imigwi y'abagore
" Ubu ari mu mugwi nserukiragihugu w'Uburundi ishitse mu nkino za nyuma ubwa mbere, n'aho atashoboye gukina inkino zibiri za mbere, yose umugwi wiwe watsinzwemwo, ariko aranezererewe no kuba yaragiye muri Maroc muri iryo higanwa
 Uwo mukinyi wo hagati agira ati:"Sinigeze nibaza ko nzoshika ngaha
 Narakoze cane, naranezerewe cane banshize ku rutonde
" Habonimana akina mu mugwi wo ku mugwa mukuru w'ubutunzi, i Bujumbura mu Burundi
 Nk'umwana muto mu muryango, ku myaka 12 yaciye atangura kwigishwa umupira na se wiwe na basaza biwe na bo basanzwe bakina umupira
 Habimana asigura ati:"Nahora nsohoka njanye na basaza banje - misi yose naguma ndabasaba kumvyura mu gihe nasinziriye, igihe baba bagiye tugaca tujana
" "Umusi umwe, umugore umwe afise umugwi w'umupira w'amaguru w'abagore yarambonye ndiko ndakina mu bagabo, aca ansaba kuja mu mugwi w'abagore, hanyuma yaciye aza muhira aravugana n'abavyeyi banje
" Umunezero w'uko Habonimana amenye ko hariho imigwi y'abagore wamaze umwanya urume rumara kuko nyina wiwe ntiyamushigikiye muri urwo rukino
 Yibuka ibi:"Mawe yambwiye -'Sindigera mbona abagore bakina umupira w'amaguru, kubera iki guma wihatira kuwukina?"  "Yambwira ko adashaka ko nkina umupira w'amaguru kubera noca nkomera cane nk'abahungu, ariko data aramubwira 'reka umwana yikinire'" "Prezida w'imigwi y'abagore y'umupira w'amaguru yaraje aravugana na mawe amubwira ko hariho abagore bakina umupira w'amaguru kandi ko atari ibintu bibi
 Hari abagore bafise abana ariko babandanya gukina, hanyuma mawe aratinda aragondozwa arandeka ndakina
" Amakenga ya nyina wa Habonimana ku bagore bakina umupira w'amaguru arumvikana kuko gukina umupira w'amaguru ku abapfasoni mu Burundi bitanguye vuba
 Ico gihugu cakinye urukino rwa mbere rwemewe na FIFA mu 2016, ariko carateye imbere cane muri iyi myaka itandatu iheze inyuma yo kuronka imfashanyo z'amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu igenewe guteza imbere umupira w'amaguru ku bapfasoni
 Uwo muyabaga yizeye ko ishirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru mu Burundi rizobandanya gukora mu ntumbero yo guteza imbere umupira w'amaguru ku bagore mu gihugu ciwe, ariko Habonimana aza yamaze gutangura kurota kujana ubumenyi afise muri urwo rukino mu bindi bihugu
 Avuga ati:"Ndizera ko nshobora gukina umupia mu bindi bihugu kuko ntushobora gutera imbere ugumye mu kibanza kimwe
" Gukinira Uburundi, buri mu kibanza kiri hasi cane mu vyitavye iryo higanwa (buri mu kibanza ca 169 kuri bihugu  181 biri ku rutonde rwa Fifa), muri Wafcon bishobora muri kazoza kumufasha gushika ku ndoto ziwe, kandi uravye imyaka yiwe, arashobora kubishikako
 Gutsindwa n'iyindi migwi mishasha, Botswana 4-2 mu rukino rwa mbere, gutsindwa na Afrika y'Epfo 3-1, yabaye iya kabiri mw'ihiganwa riheruka, vyari vyitezwe ariko bisize uwo mugwi habi

Ukraine itegekanya "abasirikare umuliyoni" bitwaje ibigwanisho yahawe na Otan mu kwisubiza ubumanuko bw'igihugu bwigaruriwe n'Uburusiya nk'uko bivugwa n'umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi
 Oleksii Reznikov avuga ko ukwisubiza uturere dukikuje inkengera z'ikiyaga cirabura ari ngombwa ku butunzi bw'ico gihugu
 Ariko ayo majambo asa nk'akamo ariko aratera gusumba umugambi nyezina nk'uko bivugwa n'umumenyeshamakuru wa BBC ari i Kyiv Joe Inwood
 Ayo majambo y'umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi ayavuze mu gihe Uburusiya buriko buratera intambwe mu kwigarurira akarere ko mu buseruko ka Donbas
 Igitero ku nzu y'amagorofa ku musi w'Imana cahitanye abantu boba bashika 18 - hakaba hari ubwoba ko abarenga 20 boba bari musi y'ibihomoke vy'iyo nzu
 Abajejwe gutabara baracarondera aboba bagihema ahari hubatswe iyo nzu y'amagorofa atanu i Chasiv Yar, hafi y'igisagara ca Kramatorsk, mu karere ka Donetsk Uburusiya bwibanze cane mu gutera
 Mu kiganiro ciwe yahaye ikinyamakuru Times, Reznikov yashimagije cane Ubwongereza kuba bwarabaye "kirumara" mu gufasha Ukraine kuronka ibigwanisho vya Otan vyo kwikingira ibitero vy'indege ivuye kuvyahoze bikoreshwa ku ntwaro ya kisoviete
 Yavuze ko itangwa ry'ibigwanisho rikwiye kwihutishwa
 Yagize ati: "Dukeneye ibindi vyinshi, vyihuta, kugira dukingire ubuzima bw'abasirikare bacu
 Buri musi dutakaza abasirikare amajana n'amajana mu gihe turindiriye ibigwanisho bitera ibibombe
" Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi yongeyeko ati: "Tugereranije dufise abantu 700
000 mu ngabo, dushizeko abacungera umutekano mu gihugu (National guard), abapolisi n'abacungera imbibe, turashika umuliyoni
 Ariko Dr Jack Watling, umushakashatsi wo mu rwego rwo hejuru mu kigo ca Royal United Services Institute, ntiyemera ivyo ico giharuro
 Watling yabwiye BBC ati: "Si umuliyoni w'abasirikare bakomeye bazogira ibitero vyo kwisubiza uturere twanyazwe
 "Mubisanzwe wogira ibikorwa vya gisirikare bitunguranye mu gihe ushaka kugira ibitero nk'ivyo, kubimenyesha rero ku mugaragaro bisa no kuvunira akagohe Uburusiya ngo burondere ubundi buryo bwinshi kugira bwitegurire ivyo bitero
"
