 Yari yagarutse muri United mu mwaka uheze inyuma yo gukinira Real Madrid na Juventus
 Uwo yahoze amenyereza Ajax, Ten Hag agira ati:"Ntari kumwe nacu kubera imvo bwite ziwe
 Tumufiseko umugambi muri uyu mwaka
 Ni ko biri
" "Mfise igishika co gukorana na we
 Cristiano si uwo kugurisha
 Ari mu mugambi wacu
 Dushaka amahirwe turi kumwe
" Isiba ry'uwo munye Portugal muri urwo rugendo ryatumye haba ibihuha kuri kazoza kiwe, inyuma kandi yo kutagaragara mu myimenyerezo y'uwo mugwi   yo kwitegurira ihiganwa ryimirije i Carrington
 Ahubwo Ronaldo yagize imyimenyerezo n'umugwi nserukiragihu wa Portugal aho basanzwe bimenyerereza
 Manchester United izotana mu mitwe na Liverpool muri Thailand  ku musi wa kabiri imbere yo kwurira indege baja muri Australia, Ten Hag akavuga ko ataramenya nimba Ronaldo azobasangayo mu nyuma
 Uwo mumenyereza w'umudagi yongeyeko ko yavuganye na Ronaldo imbere y'urwo rugendo, asigura:"Twayaze neza
