" Ten Hag  yagize kandi ico acuga kuvyerekeye uwoba kizigenza, cabaye ikibazo kuva mu mwaka uheze kubera Harry Maguire adahagaze neza
 Yagize ati: "Harry Maguire azoba kizigenza
 Amaze umwaka urenga ari kizigenza
 Amaze gushika kuri vyinshi
 Nta nkeka mfise kuri ivyo
" Umukinyi wenyene United imaze kuzana muri iri ci n'umukinyi w'inyuma Tyrell Malacia yakuye mu mugwi wa Feyenoord
 Biteze kunaza umukinyi w'inyuma Christian Eriksen ata n'urumeya bamutanzeko, bakaba kandi begereje kugiriranira amasezerano na Barcelone ku mukinyi Frenkie de Jong
 Ten Hag yacishijemwo avuga ko United izozana abakinyi mu gihe ibonye ko bahuje uko bakina
 Yongeyeko ati:"Dushaka kwongeramwo abakinyi babikwiye
 Dufise umugwi mwiza cane, turiko turakora mu guteza imbere uburyo dukina, kandi akaryo karahari tuzotsinda
"
Umukuru w’igihugu ca Sri Lanka Gotabaya Rajapaksa yatangaje ko agiye gutanga imihoho inyuma y’aho abari mu myiyerekano nijoro batereye ikirimba ciwe bakanaturira inzu y’umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Yaba umushikiranganji wa mbere, yaba umukuru w’igihugu, nta n’umwe yari muhira igihe ii vyaba
 Amajana n’amajana y’abari mu myiyerekano barihaye amabarabara ku mugwa mukuru Colombo, basaba ko Rajapaksa ava ku butegetsi inyuma y’imyiyerekano imaze amezi atari make biyamiriza isesagura ry’ubutunzi
 Perezida Rajapaksa ategekanya gutanga imihoho ku wa 13 Mukakaro (uku kwezi kw’indwi), ni ukuvuga ku wa gatatu
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Wickremesinghe na we nyene yemeye gutanga imihoho
 Umukuru w’inama nshingamateka avuga ko umukuru w’igihugu yafashe ingingo yo gutanga imihoho “kugira ngo ashikirize ubutegetsi mu mahoro” anatera akamo abanyagihugu “kwubaha amategeko”
 Amaze gutangaza iyi ngingo, igisagara cose cuzuye akanyamuneza
 Inyuma y’ivyaraye bibaye nijoro ku wa gatandatu, Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zasavye ubutegetsi bwa Sri Lanka gukora ningoga kugira ngo batorere umuti izi ngorane zishingiye ku butunzi muri ico gihugu
 Umwe mu bari mu myiyerekano, Fiona Sirmana, yari mu bateye inkirimba, avuga ko hageze “kwikurako umukuru w’igihugu n’umushikiranganji wa mbere tugatangura ibihe bishasha muri Sri Lanka”
 Yabwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Reuters ati: “Numva mbabaye, ndababaye cane kubera batahavuye hakiri kare kuko iyo bagenda hakiri kare nta vyari kwononekara”
 Mu myiyerekano y’ejo ku wa gatandatu, hari abatari bake bakomeretse, umuvugizi w’ibitaro bikuru vya Colombo akaba yabwiye itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP ko abantu batatu bariko baravurwa ibikomere vy’amasasu
 Sri Lanka iri mu bibazo vy’ifaranga ryataye agaciro bikomeye, bikaba bitayoroheye kwinjiza ibifungurwa, ibitoro n’imiti, ibikuye hanze, mu gihe igihugu gihanzwe n’ingorane z’ubutunzi itari bwigere ibaho mu myaka 70
 Yaherewe n’amafaranga mvamakungu, bica biba ngombwa ko ibuza igurishwa ry’iresansi (essence) n’amazutu ku mamodoka y’abigenga, ivyatumye haba imirongo miremire imaze imisi y’abarondera igitoro
 Ivyaraye bibaye nijoro, ibintu bidasanzwe, bisa n’ivyerekana ko ibintu vyayangaye mu myiyerekano y’amahoro yari imaze amezi muri Sri Lanka
 Isinzi ry’abantu bahuriye ku kirimba c’umukuru w’igihugu Rajapaksa, baririmba ivyivugo, bafise n’ibendera ry’igihugu imbere y’uko basenyura uruzitiro bakinjira muri iyo nyubakwa
 Amavidewo yazungurutse ku mbuga hwaniro yerekana abantu bitera muri ico kirimba, boga muri pisine (piscine) y’umukuru w’igihugu, mu gihe abandi nabo bariko bayora ivyari mu bubati, basaka amatungo ya perezida mbere banakoresha ubwogero bwiwe bw’agahebuza
 Ubudasa hagati y’iki kirimba giteye igomwe n’amezi iki gihugu c’imiriyoni 22 z’abantu kimaze mu bibazo ntibwaciye mu ryahumye abari mu myiyerekano
 Chanuka Jayasuriya  yabwiye Reuters ati: "Abantu baje kwimara ishavu kubera igihugu kiri mu ngorane nk’izi
 Iyo ubonye ivyiza vy’akaroruhore muri ino nzu, biragaragara neza ko aba bantu ata mwanya bafise wo gukorera igihugu”
 Amakuru atangwa na Reuters avuga ko ku wa gatanu Perezida Rajapaksa yavuye mu kirimba ciwe mu kwicungera amaze kwumva ko hari imigumuko yari itegekanijwe, nk’uko amasoko abiri yo mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi abivuga
 N’aho ari ikirimba ca Rajapaksa, akunze kwirarira mu yindi nzu iri mu micungararo
 BBC ntirashobora kumenya aho umukuru w’igihugu yinyegeje
 Abari mu myiyerekano kandi baturiye inzu y’umushikiranganji wa mbere Wickremesinghe yiwe bwite iri muri karitiye y’abakire i Colombo
 Imbere y’aho, yari yatangaje ko yari afise ishaka ryo gutanga imihoho kugira ngo abanyagihugu ntibagwe mu mporero, be no kugira ngo atange inzira yo gushinga reta ihuriyemwo imigambwe yose, ariko haciye akanya gato atangaje ibi haciye hatangura gukwiragizwa amavidewo y’inzu yiwe iriko irasha
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere yabana n’umuryango wiwe mu nzu yiwe bwite akaba yari asanzwe akoresha ikirimba ciwe mu bikorwa vy’igihugu gusa
 Ntibiramenyekana neza nimba iyi mihoho y’umukuru w’igihugu n’umushikiranganji wa mbere ikwiye kugira ngo imyiyerekano icurehe
 Bhavani Fonseka, umunyamategeko azwi cane mu vyo guharanira agateka ka zina muntu i Colombo, avuga ati: "Imihoho y’abantu babiri bonyene ntihagije, kuko abantu basaba ko ibintu bihinduka mu butegetsi, ariko n’imiburiburi iyi ni intango mu gihe umukuru w’igihugu n’umushikiranganji wa mbere bogenda”
 Uyu mupfasoni avuga ati: "Ni ngombwa ko haba uguhererekana ubutegetsi mu mahoro, ibi navyo ntavyo turabona”

Abantu n’imiburiburi 15 ni bo bapfuye abandi hafi 20 bakaba bashobora kuba baguweko n’ibihomoka inyuma y’aho ibisasu vya roketi bisamburiye inzu isanzwe ituwemwo n’abantu mu gisagara ca Chasiv Yar, igisagara kiri mu buseruko bwa Ukraine, nk’uko abategetsi babivuga
 Abantu batanu bashoboye kurokorwa bagikomye
 Iki gitigiri c’abapfuye catanzwe n’abajejwe ubutabazi
 Veronika Bakhal wo mu gisata kijejwe ubutabazi i Donetsk yabwiye BBC ko abantu n’imiburiburi bakizibiriwe mu bihomoka, harimwo n’umwana umwe
 Avuga ati: "Twashoboye kuvugana n’abantu batatu bakiri mu bihomoka kandi tubandanya tuvugana
 "Ibi bisigura neza ko hariyo abantu bakiri bazima
 Hariko harafatwa ingingo yo kubatabara”
 Uruhande rumwe rw’iyi nyubakwa y’igorofa zitanu rwasambutse, bituma haba ikirundo c’ibihomoka
 Chasiv Yar iri hafi ya Kramatorsk mu ntara ya Donetsk
 Donetsk niyo Uburusiya bwiziziye mu ntambara yabwo muri Ukraine
 Buramatari w’iyi ntara Pavlo Kyrylenko avuga ko roketi zizwi nka Uragan ari zo zasambuye iyi nyubakwa
 Mu bumanuko, ingabo za Ukraine zateye ibisasu vya misire kuri uno wa Mungu mu gisagara kiri mu minwe y’ingabo z’Uburusiya ca Kherson
 Amakuru atangwa n’impande zompi aratandukanye: umutegetsi wa Ukraine avuga ko ikirindiro c’ingabo z’Uburusiya ari co catewe, mu gihe amakuru atangwa n’Uburusiya nayo avuga ko ibitaro hamwe n’inzu ari vyo vyononekaye
 Serhiy Bratchuk, umutegetsi wa Ukraine ari mu gisagara ca Odesa, avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine “zateye ikirindiro c’abateye igihugu cabo mu ntara ya Kherson”, akaba yasohoye n’isanamu yerekana umwotsi mwinshi hejuru ya Kherson
 Itororokanirizo ry’amakuru ry’Uburusiya Tass rivuga ko ingabo zirwanira mu kirere i Kherson zishuye, hakaba humvikanye ibiturika bine muri ico gisagara
 Iki kinyamakuru kivuga ko igisasu ca misire catewe n’ingabo za Ukraine casambuye inzu, gikomeretsa n’abantu babiri
 Ikinyamakuru co mu Burusiya gikorera ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi Khersonsky Vyestnik kivuga ko ibitaro vyononekaye muri ico gitero ca Ukraine
 BBC ntiyashoboye guhinyuza ivyononekariye muri ico gitero ca misire

Inyuma y’imyaka irenga 20 ari ku butegetsi, umukuru w’igihugu c’u Rwanda avuga ko azokwihweza ko yobandanya yitoza ngo arongore iki gihugu mu yindi myaka 20
 Paul Kagame yemereye imboneshakure y’Abafaransa ko ashobora gusubira kwitoza mu matora yimirije mu 2024
 Mu  2015 yahinduye ibwirizwashingiro, rikaba rimuha uburenganzira bwo kuguma ku butegetsi gushika mu 2034
 Mu matora y’umukuru w’igihugu aheruka haraciye imyaka itanu, ibiharuro bitangwa bivugwa ko yatsinze ku rugero rwa 99% vy’amajwi yose, ivyo abenshi mu bari hanze y’igihugu babona nk’amanyanga
 Abajijwe nimba azosubira kwitoza, Perezida Kagame, ubu afise imyaka 64, avuga ati: "Nzokwihweza ko nokwitoza no mu yindi myaka 20
 Jewe nta ngorane mfise kuri ico
 Amatora ni abanyagihugu bahitamwo”
 Umuyobozi wa Human Rights Watch muri Afrika yo hagati, Lewis Mudge, yabwiye BBC ati "Igitangaje ni uko abantu bamwe batangara"
 Ati: "Urwanda ni igihugu aho kizira kikaziririzwa kuvuguruza reta…tureke kuba uwutavuga rumwe muri poritike…kandi ubu butegetsi bw’agahotoro buzobandanya no muri kazoza ka hafi”
 Umwe mu banyarwanda bakomeye anegura u Rwanda yanakoresheje amajambo akomeye
 Charles Kambanda , umunyamategeko akaba n’umwigisha wa kaminuza ubu aba muri Amerika, yabwiye BBC ati: "Mu gihe yobandanya iyindi myaka 20, u Rwanda ruzoba umuriro udahera”
 Kambanda avuga ko Abanyarwanda basanzwe baba mu bwoba, mbere avuga ko abashikiranganji barenga umwe bamubwiye ko baguma muri reta kuko batinya ko bohava bicwa mu gihe boyivamwo
 Hagati aho, Perezifa Kagame yarashigikiye cane intambwe Urwanda rugezeko mu bijanye n’agateka ka zina muntu, igihe haba ikoraniro rya Commonwealth ku mugwa mukuru Kigali muri Ruheshi (6)
 Amezi make imbere y’aha, ni ukuvuga mu kwa kane, Ubwongereza bwatangaje integuro itabonwa kumwe yo kurungika mu Rwanda bamwe mu basaba ubuhungiro binjira ku butaka bwabwo, kugira Basabe ubuhungiro muri iki gihugu co muri Afrika y’ibiyaga binini
 Iyi ngingo yariyamirijwe n’ishirahamwe ONU riyigereranya “n’urudandaza”, ariko ibiro vy’umushikiranganji wa mbere vyiyemeje kubandanya n’uwu mugambi n’aho Boris Johnson agiye kugenda
 Perezida Kagame ari mu butegetsi kuva mu 1994, inyuma y’aho umuhari wa FPR-Inkotanyi - ubu ukaba ari wo mugambwe uri ku butgetsi -  ufatiye igihugu mu 1994 inyeshamba zawo yari arongoye zibanje gutuza jesonide
 Ico gihe yabaye icegera c’uwari umukuru w’igihugu Pasteur Bizimungu yahavuye atanga imihoho mu 2000, Paul Kagame agaca amusubirira, kuva ico gihe akaba ari we aramutswa igihugu
 Perezida Kagame aboneka nk’umutegetsi yashikanye igihugu kw’iterambere rikomeye kuva shitse ku butegetsi, ariko abamunegura bavuga ko abandanya kwifatira mu minwe ico babona nk’ubutegetsi bw’agahotoro

Abantu n’imiburiburi 15 nibo bishwe barashwe mu kabare kari mu gisagara ca Soweto muri Afrika y’Epfo, nk’uko igipolisi kibitangaza
 Igipolisi kivuga ko abantu bitwaje inkoho binjiye mu kabare ka Orlando East  mu masaha yo mu gatondo ko kuri uno musi wa Mungu baca batangura kurasa mu rudavagi mu murwi w’urwaruka rwari ruhari
 Baciye bahunga n’imodoka
 Igipolisi kivuga ko imvo y’iki gitero itaramenyekana
 Abandi bantu batari bake bakomeretse cane bakaba bariko baravurirwa mu bitaro, nk’uko umunyamakuru wa BBC Nomsa Maseko abivuga
 Abakorewe ubu bukozi bw’ikibi bavugwa ko bari hagati y’imyaka 19 na 35
 Umukuru w’igipolisi mu ntara ya Gauteng Liyetena-Jenerali Elias Mawela, yabwiye BBC ko iki gitero gisa n’ic’ubunyamaswa ku nzirakarengane zikunda gusororera muri aka kabare”
 Itangazo ryasohowe n’ibiro vyiwe rivuga ko aba bantu binjiye muri ako kabare bafise inkoho nini hamwe na ntonto
 Abapolisi bariko barahiga aba bantu gushika ubu bataramenyekna abo ari bo, nk’uko iri tangazo rivibuga
 Igipolisi kivuga kandi ko abandi bantu bane bishwe mu kindi gitero c’inkoho nyene mu kabare kari mu ntara ya KwaZulu-Natal iri mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Afrika y’Epfo
 Ivyo kurasana muri Afrika y’Epfo ni ibintu bimenyerewe
 Akenshi bifitaniye isano n’imirwi y’inkozi z’ikibi canke inzoga
 Ariko iki nico gitero gihitanye abantu benshi kandi kikaba kibaye inyuma y’imisi mike imiyabaga 21 ipfuye aho vyavuzwe ko yoba yatewe imyuka canke igahabwa isumu mu kandi kabare nyene mu gisagara ca East London

