Ibitero vya rokete n’ibisasu vya misire vyononye ibitari bike mu bisagara vyo mu buseruko no mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine, nk’uko abategetsi b’akarere babivuga
 Abasivire bane barapfuye mu gitero cabaye mu gisagara ca Siversk mu ntara ya  Donetsk, nk’uko buramatari Pavlo Kyrylenko abivuga
 Uturere dutuwemwo n’abasivire twa Druzhkivka muri iyi ntara nyene natwo nyene twaratewe
 Inyubakwa y’akaguriro yarasambuwe no mu micungararo hasigara ikinogo kinini
 BBC ntiyashoboye guhinyuza ibivugwa kuri ibi bitero biheruka
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya zirwanira hasi zisa n’izitashoboye gutera intambwe ikomeye mu masaha 24 arangiye mu rugamba rwazo rwo kwigarurira igice gisigaye c’intara ya Donetsk
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine kandi bavuga ko ibisasu vya misire vyatewe mu turere twa Kharkiv mu buraruko, Mykolaiv mu bumanuko, na Kryvyi Rih, igisagara kiri mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Mykolaiv
 Ingabo za Ukraine ziriko zirarwana n’inguvu zazo zose mu gukingira Mykolaiv, igisagara gikomeye kiri ku nkengera  y’uruzi kw’ibarabara rikomeye rija i Odesa, igisagara nyamukuru Ukraine icishako ibidandazwa ishora hanze
 Amato y’intambara y’Uburusiya aracabuza Ukraine gushora hanze intete ziva i Odesa
 Icegera c’umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Ukraine Iryna Vereshchuk asaba abanyagihugu kuva mu duce twigaruriwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya mu bisagara vya Kherson na Zaporizhzhia mu bumanuko
 Aka kamo gasa n’akerekana ko ingabo za Ukraine zoba ziriko zitegura ibindi bitero vyo kwivuna
 Abarusiya barigaruriye igisagara ca Kherson, ariko ingabo za Ukraine zarashoboye kwisubiza uduce tumwe tumwe tw’ako karere
 Igipolisi muri iyo ntara cagiriza Uburusiya guhonya n’ibigirankana ibiterwa
 Mu butumwa cacishije ku rubuga rwa Facebook, cerekana imirima iriko irasha, kikavuga kiti: “Imiriro myinshi yama yaduka uko bukeye uko bwije, amajana n’amajana y’amahegitari y’ingano, hamwe n’izindi ntete aramaze guturirwa”
 Cagiriza kandi ingabo z’Uburusiya gusambura ibigega n’ibikoresho vyo mu burimyi, kandi zikanabuza abanyagihugu kuzimya iyi miriro
  I Kryvyi Rih, vya muzinga vyarononye ishure n’inzu y’uburaro, vyica umugore w’imyaka 41, nk’uko bivugwa na buramatari Valentyn Reznichenko
 Ubushikiranganji bw’Uburusiya bujejwe kwivuna abansi buvuga ko ingabo zabwo zabomoye ikigangara cari kibitswemwo ibirwanisho vyo mu bwoko bwa M777 vyatanzwe na Amerika i Chasiv Yar hafi ya Kramatorsk
 Slovyansk na Kramatorsk vyitezwe kuba ibindi bisagara nyamukuru gukiririmbirwamwo n’Uburusiya muri Donetsk
 Amerika ivuga ko igiye kurungikira Ukraine ibindi birwanisho bidahusha bitera ibisasu vya rokete
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko ibisasu vya muzinga vyo mu bwoko bwa HIMARS  biriko birakoreshwa mu gutera ububiko bw’ibirwanisho mu turere turi mu minwe y’Uburusiya, ibituma Moscou itoroherwa na gato mu kurungika ibindi
 Mu Bwongereza, ibigo vya gisirikare biriko birakoreshwa mu kwigisha ingabo za Ukraine ubuhinga bwo kurwana, nk’uko reta y’Ubwogereza ibivuga
 Ni mu ntumbero yo kwigisha abanya-Ukraine 10
000 mu mezi ari imbere
 Mu yandi makuru y’igendereza, igisirikare c’Ubwongereza kivuga ko Uburusiya buriko buregeranya izindi ngabo mu gihugu cose buzegereza hafi ya Ukraine mu kwitegurira ibindi bitero

Uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wo kurwanya ubusumbasumbane Kemi Badenoch niwe aherutse kuja ku rutonde rw’abashingamateka b’aba Conservateurs/Conservative bari mu rugamba rwo kurongora uyu mugambwe no kuba umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Igihe amenyesha iyi ngingo yo guhiganira iki kibanza mu kinyamakuru Times, uyu mushingamateka Badenoch - afise amamuko ku bavyeyi b’abanya-Nigeria - avuga ko yipfuza kugabanya inguvu za reta be no “kuvuga ukuri”
 Umukandida akomeye gushika ubu ni uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w’ikigega ca reta Rishi Sunak – yatangaje ko agiye kwiyamamariza iki kibanza ku wa gatanu
 Uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa Brexit Steve Baker avuga ko atazoja mu bahiganira iki kibanza, akaba yatangaje ko azoshigikira umushikirizamanza mukuru Suella Braverman
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Boris Johnson aherutse gutanga imihoho muri ino ndwi inyuma y’aho abashikiranganji batari bake bavumburiye muri reta yiwe avuga ko ashaka kuguma ku butegetsi gushika hatowe uwumusubirira
 Mu bandi bavuga ko bashaka guhiganira iki kibanza kugira bamusubirire, harimwo uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu Sajid Javid, umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi Ben Wallace, n’uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire Jeremy Hunt
 Ikirangamisi ku vyerekeye uguhiganira kurongora uyu mugambwe, uzwi kandi nka Tory, citezwe kwemezwa mu ndwi iza, umushikiranganji wa mbere mushasha akaba yitezwe mu kw’icenda
 Ashikiriza imigambi yiwe mu nkuru yacishijwe mu kinyamakuru The times, Badenoch  avuga ko hakenewe “reta ikomeye ariko ifise ububasha bugereranye, yitaho ivya nkenerezwa”
 Uyu mushingamateka w’imyaka 42 aserukira akarere ka Saffron Walden – akaba yari mu bashikiranganji batanze imihoho muri ino ndwi – avuga ko azogabanya amakori, ariko kandi “acungere ikoreshwa ry’amafaranga”
 "Ata mpinduka zibaye mu mugambwe w’aba Conservateurs, Ubwongereza hamwe n’ibindi bihugu vy’Uburengero bizobandanya bitakaza inguvu” kandi abakeba “bazoduca imbere mu butunzi mbere baturushe n’amayeri ku rwego mpuzamakungu”, niko yandika
 "Nje guharanira ubu burongozi muri ano matora kubera nshaka gushikiriza ukuri
 Ukuri ni kwo kuzoturokora”
 Avuga ko “abanyagihugu baruhishijwe n’ubujambo bwo kubahendahenda ata kirimwo” kandi ko abantu “badatahura ivya nkenererwa mu kurongora igihugu”
 Mu kiringo ciwe nk’umushikiranganji ajejwe kurwanya ubusumbasumbane, Badenoch  yaraneguwe n’umurwi mpanuzwajambo wa reta w’abari muri wa murwi w’abahuza ibitsina babisangiye, hari mu kwa gatatu, kubera yari yatebeje guhagarika umugambi wo guhindura abantu bari muri uyu murwi, ikizwi nka conversion therapy
 Ku wa gatatu yaratanze imihoho ari kumwe n’abandi bane bakorana, mw’iteke bandikiye hamwe akaba yavuga ko atanze imihoho mu mabanga yiwe “mu mubabaro mwinshi”
 Fyonda aho musi wumvirize ingene Boris Johnson yavuze igihe atanga imihoho:
Umurwi wa mbere w’ingabo za Ukraine watanguye inyigisho za gisirikare nshasha mu Bwongereza mu ntumbero yo gufasha ico gihugu kurwanya ingabo z’Uburusiya zateye igihugu cabo
 Abasirikare ba Ukraine bagera kuri 10
000 nibo bazoronswa izi nyigisho ku birindiro bitandukanye vy’ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi mu gihugu cose mu mezi make ari imbere
 Uyu mugambi uzofasha abitangira igihugu cabo kuronka ubuhinga bukenewe bwo kurwana ku rubuga rw’intambara, nk’uko ubu bushikiranganji bubivuga
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi Ben Wallace avuga ko iyi yari yo “ntambwe ikurikira” mu twigoro tw’Uwongereza two gufata mu mugongo ingabo za Ukraine
 Abasirikare bababa 1050 b’Ubwongereza nibo bahawe iki gikorwa co kwigisha ingabo za Ukraine ku bigo bitandukanye mu gihugu cose – ku birometero birenga 1600 uvuye ku rubuga rw’intambra mu karere ka Donbas mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 Uwu mugambi w’Ubwongereza ufise intumbero yo kwigisha abanya-Ukraine gushika ku 10
000 mu misi 120, ariko “bibaye ngombwa bazokwiyongera”, nk’uko umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi abivuga
 Ati: "Turi mu minwe y’abanya -Ukraine
 "Dukoresheje ubuhinga karuhariwe kw’isi bw’igisirikare c’Ubwongereza, tuzofasha Ukraine kunagura igisirikare cayo tubongerereze n’ubushobozi bwo kwivuna mu gihe bariko bararwanira ubwigenge bw’igihugu cabo be n’uburenganzira bwo kwihitiramwo ku vyerekeye kazoza kabo”
 Ibi vyigwa bishingiye ku nyigisho shingiro z’igisirikare c’Ubwongereza, harimwo gukoresha ibirwanisho, ubutabazi bwihuta ku rubuga rw’intambara, kwiga akarere, amayeri yo gukizura hamwe n’amategeko ajanye n’intambara ya gisirikare
 Ingabo za Ukraine zababa 22
000 ziramaze kwigishwa n’Ubwongereza mu ciswe, Operation Orbital, hagati ya 2015 na 2022
