Igipolisi kiriko kirakora amatohoza kw’igandagurwa ry’uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubuyapani Shinzo Abe kivuga ko yari asanzwe afitiye umujinya “ishirahamwe runaka”
 Uyu yagirizwa ubu bwicanyi, azwi kw’izina rya Tetsuya Yamagami w’imyaka 41, yari azi ko Abe yari muri iri shirahamwe nyene kandi ko yamwishe kubera ico, nk’uko abakora amatohoza babivuga, ariko bakaba badatanga izina ry’iri shirahamwe
 Abe yapfiriye mu bitato ejo ku wa gatanu inyuma y’aho arasiwe ariko ashikiriza ijambo mu myiyamamazo
 Yamagami aremera ko yamurashe akoresheje inkoho yakorewe muhira, nk’uko igipolisi kibivuga
 Abe yari we mushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubuyapani yamaze ikirongo kirekire, urupfu rwiwe rukaba rwababaje iki gihugu cari gisanzwe kitavugwamwo ubukozi bw’ikibi hakoreshejwe inkoho
 Yarashwe ariko yamamariza uwari umugambwe wiwe, Liberal Democratic Party (LDP), mu matora y’inama nkenguzamateka ategekanijwe ejo ku wa Mungu
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Fumio Kishida, na we nyene akaba ari umunywanyi w’umugambwe LDP, avuga ko yabuze “n’ico avuga” kuri uru rupfu rwa Abe, akavuga ko intwaro rusangi y’Ubuyapani “idashobora namba kusubizwa inyuma n’ubukozi bw’ikibi”
 Avuga ko imyiyamamazo ibandanya ukuri kwamye kuri uno wa gatandatu mu gihe umutekano ucungerewe bikomeye, kandi ko n’amatora ategekanijwe kuri uyu wa Mungu azoba ukuri kwamye
