Umuvugizi w'umushikiranganji wa mbere w'Ubwongereza Boris Johnson yavuze ko reta ifise umugambi wo kubandanya politike zumvikanyweko harimwo kurungika abimukira mu Rwanda
 Ico kiganiro ku bamenyeshamakuru cabereye ku biro iwe kibaye inyuma y'aho Johnson atangiye imihoho mu mabanga yo kurongora umugambwe w'aba Conservateurs, ariko akazoguma mu mabanga y'umushikiranganji wambere gushika hatowe uwundi aramutswa ayo mabanga
 Ivyo bishobora kudafata amezi menshi kubera Johnson ashobora kutazokoresha umwanya asigaranye nk'umushikiranganji wa mbere mu "kugira ico ahinduye mu ntumbero ya politike yiwe"
 Ni muri iyo ntumbero umuvugizi wiwe yavuze ko politike yo gutwara abimukira mu Rwanda, yamenyeshejwe  na reta mu kwezi kwa kane, ishobora kubandanya
 Ifise intumbero yo gufata bamwe mu bimukira bajabutse Manche binjira mu Bwongereza kujanwa mu gihugu c'Urwanda gusabirayo ubuhungiro, hakubusabira mu Bwongereza
 Ariko gushika ubu nta n'umwe ararungikwa mu Rwanda ava mu Bwongereza
 Indege yategerezwa kujana abo bimukira yarasibijwe imbere y'uko ihaguruka mu kwezi guheze, bivuye ku ngingo yo ku munota wa nyuma ya sentare ya Buraya ijejwe agateka ka zina muntu
 Sentare nkuru mu Bwongereza vyitezwe ko yumviriza urubanza muri uku kwezi, rwerekeye politike yo kwirukana abasaba ubuhungiro bidakurikije amategeko
 Igitangazamakuru PA casubiyemwo uwo muvugizi aho yagize ati: "Umwumvikano ntubuza canke ngo ubere intambamyi reta yo kurondera gushira mu bikorwa iyo politike harimwo no gusigura iyo ngingo muri sentare nk'uko bisabwa
" Uwo muvugizi yongeyeko ko vyashoboka ko indege igenda imbere y'urubanza ruba

Boris Johnson ararahira akarengwa ko adashobora kuva ku butegetsi n’aho abenshi mu bari bamushigikiye bamukuyeko amaboko mu gutanga imihoho mu buryo budasanzwe
 Uyu mushikiranganji wa mbere yimye amatwi abamusaba gutanga imihoho nijoro ku wa gatatu, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari soma mbike nawe, harimwo na Priti Patel na Grant Shapps
 Umunyamabanga wa reta wa Pays de Galles/Wales, Simon Hart, niwe mutegetsi wa reta yiwe yatanze imihoho ubwa nyuma, mu gihe umushikirizamanza mukuru Suella Braverman nawe yatanguye kwihweza ibintu bitagenda neza mu butegetsi
 Ariko umushikirangaji wa mbere ashimangira ko abamutoye bamuhaye "amabanga akomeye ategerezwa kubandanya"
 Mu guhangana n’abamurwanya, umushikiranganji wa mbere yabogoje umunyamabanga yari ajejwe imibereho myiza n’uburinganire Michael Gove mu buryo butangaje, aho isoko rimwe ryo mu biro vy’umushikiranganji wa mbere ryamwise “inzoka” igenda “yigamba imbere y’ibinyamakuru ko yabwiye umushikiranganji wa mbere kuva ku butegetsi”
 Mu masaha ya kare ejo ku wa gatatu, Gove yahoze afatanije na we muri rwa rugamba rwa Brexit rwo kuva mw'ishirahamwe rya Bulaya ariko akaza kubera intambamyi Johnson igihe yiyamamaza ubwa mbere ku burongozi bw’umugambwe w’abagendera karanga ka kera (Conservateurs/Conservative), yari yasavye umushikiranganji wa mbere gutanga imihoho
 Yirukanywe ku mugoroba wa nijoro inyuma y’aho abashikiranganji n’ivyegera barenga 40 batangiye imihoho – ibitari bwigere bibaho mu kiringo c’amasaha 24
 Eka no mu masaha y’ijoro, abatanga imihoho barabandanije, aho umunyamabanga wa Pays de Galles Hart yagiye gukura akarenge imbere gato y’isaha zitanu z’ijoro mu masaha y’Ubwongereza
 Hart avuga ko ata yindi nzira yari asigaranye, yongerako y’uko bagenziwe bakoze ivyo bashobora vyose, haba mu mwiherero canke ku mugaragaro, mu “kugufasha guhindura ibintu, ariko numva agahinda kubona igihe carenze kugira ibi bishoboke”
 Yari umwe mu murwi w’abashikiranganji bagerageje guhanura umushikiranganji wa mbere gutanga imihoho, harimwo mbere n’abahoze ari soma mbike na Johnson nka Patel, umushikiranganji w'intwaro yo hagati mu gihugu, hamwe n'umushikiranganji wo gutwara abantu n’ibintu Shapps, n’umushikiranganji w’ubudandaji Kwasi Kwarteng
 Mu gihe ari mu ngorane zidasanzwe z’ubutegetsi bwiwe, umushikiranganji wa mbere Johnson ari mu kibazo co gusubiriza abashikiranganji bababa 20 inyuma y’abatanze imihoho ku bwinshi
 Mu masaha yitereye ya nijoro ku wa gatatu, umushikirizamanza mukuru Braverman  yahoze ari soma mbike yifatanije n’abandi mu gutera akamo Johnson ko yotanga imihoho, aho yabwiye umunyamakuru Peston w’imboneshakure ITV ko yagiye avyitwaramwo “nabi cane” muri ino misi ya vuba
 Avuga ko adashobora gutanga imihoho kubera ari ngombwa ko abandanya n’amabanga yiwe ariko akavuga ati: “Mu gihe hoba uguhiganira uburongozi, noshiramwo izina ryanje”
 Uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w’amagara y’abantu Matt Hancock nawe yakuye icizere ku mushikiranganji wa mbere, avuga ko yamushigikiye “mu bihe bigoye n’ivyoroshe”, ariko ko ubu hageze ko agenda
 Hancock, n’aho avuga ko atazoja mu bahiganira iki kibanza c’ubutegetsi, abona ko Johnson adasigaje igihe kirekire ku butegetsi, “n’aho hoba ejo canke mu ndwi iza”
 Ariko hari bamwe mu bashikiranganji bacifatanije na we – harimwo icegera c’umushikiranganji wa mbere, Dominic Raab, umushikiranganji w’imico kama Nadine Dorries, umushikiranganji ajejwe Brexit Jacob Rees-Mogg
 Asigura igituma Johnson ategerezwa kubandanya n’amabanga yiwe, isoko rimwe ryo mu biro vyiwe rivuga riti: "Umushikiranganji wa mbere yizewe n’imiriyoni 14 z’abanyagihugu bashaka ko abakorera…nimba abanyamugambwe bashaka kumuhagarika, ni babanze bamwake iki cizere”
 Umushikiranganji mbere yararokotse mu matora y’abashingamateka yo kuraba nimba acizigiwe canke atacizigiwe mu kwezi guheze kandi nk’uko amategeko abivuga ubu, nta yandi ashobora kuba imbere y’amezi 12
 Ariko hari amatora yimirije mu ndwi iza ku burongozi bw’umurwi uzwi nka Comité 1922/1922, umurwi ugizwe n’abashingamateka b’umugambwe w’aba Conservateurs (umugambwe wa Johnson), ari na wo utegura amatora yo kuraba nimba umutegetsi kanaka acizewe canke atacizewe
 Abamurwanya bariko bashaka gutorwa mu ntumbero yo kuraba ingene amategeko yohinduka maze hagategurwa ayandi matora vuba bishoboka yo kuraba nimba acizigiwe canke atacizigiwe
 Urukurikirane rw’imihoho yo ku wa kabiri no ku wa gatatu yaturutse ku makuru y’ingene umushikiranganji atavyifashemwo neza ku kibazo c’ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina ryagirizwa uwahoze ari icegera c’umukuru w’urwego rujejwe inyifato, Chris Pincher
 Mu gihe abarongoye umugambwe bohindura iyi ngingo ibuza ko haba ayandi matora yo kuraba nimba umutegetsi acizewe canke atacizewe imbere y‘ikiringo c’umwaka, abanywanyi b’umugambwe w'aba Conservateurs barwanya Johnson bashobora kugerageza kurondera ingene bomwomora muri rino ci canke inyuma y’aho gato imbere y’igihe c'ubukonje bwinshi
 Iyo Johnson atakaza icizere c’abashingamateka, yategerezwa gutanga imihoho canke agatumako amatora
 Yotegerejwe gutanga imihoho we nyene ubwiwe – bigashoboka ku gitsure ca reta yiwe, nk’uko vyagendeye Margaret Thatcher – canke inyuma y’urundi rukurikirane rw’abashikiranganji botanga imihoho

Umushikiranganji wa mbere Boris Johnson yamenyesheje ko azotanga imihoho, bisigura ko ubu hagiye kuba amatora yo kurondera uwugiye kuba umukuru w’umugambwe w’aba Conservative n’umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Uwuzotorwa azotegerezwa gushigikirwa n’abashingamateka b’aba-Tory, abakandida babiri ba nyuma bagaca baja mw’ihiganwa mu matora yitabwa n’abanywanyi b’umugambwe w’aba Conservative
 Ariko abashobora kuba aba candida ni bande? Ingene Tom Tugendhat ateye n’igihushane ca Boris Johnson – umuntu agenza make kandi ashira imbere ibishoboka aho kuryosharyosha abanyagihugu, umugabo atakimucika yari ashigikiye kuguma mw’ishirahamwe rya Buraya mu matotora kamarampaka yo mu 2016
 Kubera ivyo, Tugendhat, yatowe nk’umushingamateka wa Tonbridge mu 2015, amaze imyaka myishi avugwa nk’uwushobora kuba indongozi y’umugambwe wa Conservative
 Kuba umukuru w’umugwi w’ijambo rikomeye ujejwe imigenderanire mu nama nshingamateka kuva mu 2020 vyatumye akomera gusumba kuko yakoresheje kahise kiwe k’umusirikare- mu gukurikirana cane ibibazo n’uruhara Ubushinwa buguma burushiriza kugira kw’isi
 Mw’ijambo ry’amarangamutima menshi ku bashingamateka,  Tugendhat yagaragaje  ishavu, umubabaro n’uburakari bw’abahoze ku rugamba kubera  abasizwe  muri Afghanistan  igihe ingabo za Buraya na Amerika zavayo gihuti huti mu kwezi k’umunani mu mwaka uheze
 Abajijwe mu 2017 niba yifuza kuba umushikiranganji wa mbere, yishuye ati : “Nyene
 Naraguze itike none kubera iki ntokwifuza gutsinda tombora (loterie)?“ Umushikirizamanza mukuru Suella Braverman hamwe na Steve Baker yari ajejewe umugambi wo kuva mw'ishirahamwe rya Buraya, nabo bompi bamaze kwerekana ko bashaka ico kibanza
 Rishi Sunak yigeze kuba abonwa na bamwe nk’uwusayanganira kuba yoba indongozi y’aba-Conservative
 Ariko muri aya mezi aheze izina ryiwe ryaratosekaye biturutse ku mpari ku bijanye n’amakori y’umugore wiwe , kandi akaba ata minsi iheze atangishijwe ihadabu ryo kurenga ku mategeko ajanye na guma mu rugo
 Yatanguye kuba umushingamateka mu 2015 – w’akarere ka North Yorkshire ya Richmond
 Uretse abo  mu nama shingamateka i Westminister , nta bandi benshi bamuzi ariko yabaye umushikiranganji ajejwe ikigega mu kwezi kwa Ruhuhuma (2)  mu 2020
 Yihuse guhangana n’ikiza ca coronavírus, asohora amafaranga menshi agerageza uko ashoboye kugira ubutunzi bugume bukora mu gihe ca guma mu rugo
 Ico gihe nticamworoheye cane kandi ntiyahavuye amenyekanye neza gusumba
 Kuba yafashe iya mbere mu gutanga imihoho muri reta hamwe na mugenziwe Sajid Javid bishobora kuba vyaciye inzira y’itangwa ry’imihoho ry’abandi benshi ryatumye amaherezo Boris Johnson agenda
 Umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire yabaye mu ba mbere mu kuvuga ko ashigikiye Johnson,  umushikiranganji ajejwe ikigega n’uwujejwe amagara bamaze gutanga imihoho, afata ikibanza gikomeye mu  bayoboka Johnson
 Nk’umugore wa kabiri yari arongoye ubushikiranganji bujejwe imigenderanire, yashimwe ku gikorwa co kurekuza Nazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe inyuma y’imyaka itandatu hamwe no gushira ibihano ku Burusiya no ku batunzi ruhebwa babwo
 Inyuma yo gutorwa ubwa mbere mu 2010 nk‘umushingamateka wa South West Norfolk , Madame Truss yabaye rurangiranwa mu banywanyi bo mu mugambwe w’aba-Conservative  kubera ivyiyumviro vyiwe vyisanzuye ku bibazo vy’ubutunzi n’ubudandaji
 Ariko uburyo bwiwe bwo gukora ntibwamye bukundwa n’abanyagihugu muri rusangi, akaba yaragawe igihe  yashikiriza ijambo mw’ikoraniro y’aba-Conservative ryo mu 2015 aho yerekanye ko ashigikiye cane  iforomaji zinjira mu Bwongereza ziva hanze
 Ariko ivyo ntivyahagaritse kubandanya atera imbere, kandi kuva ico gihe yagiye mu bibanza bitandukanye muri reta – harimwo  kwumvikana ku masezerano Ubwongereza bumaze kuva mw’ishirahamwe rya Buraya igihe yari umushikiranganji ajejwe ubudandaji mpuzamakungu – imbere y’uko ashingwa amabanga arimwo ubu
  Uwo mushingamateka wa Bromsgrove niwe yakubise irya mbere umushikiranganji wa mbere, ashimika ko hakenewe ubuziranenge kandi abwira abashingamateka mw’ijambo ryiwe ryo gutanga imihoho ko yasanze “ingorane zitangurira hejuru”
 Javid yari amaze kurondera kuba indongozi mu 2019, aho yashitse muri bane ba nyuma akavamwo kugira ashigikire Boris Johnson
 Uko kumushigikira kwashimiwe mu kugenwa kuba umushikiranganji ajejwe ikigega ca reta, ariko yaciye atanga imihoho haheze amezi atandatu mu mpari n’abajenama biwe, imbere y’uko agaruka mu buryo butangaje mu bashingamateka b’imbere mu kuba umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y’abantu mu 2021
 Umu-Conservative azi cane ibijanye n’amakori, yagumye agabisha ku  bijanye n’ingaruka mbi z’iduga ry’ibiciro n’ideni ry’igihugu, Javid yatanguye nk’umuntu abayabaye
 Yavukiye i Rochdale mu 1969 mu runganwe rwa mbere rw’umuryango w’abimukira b’abanya-Pakistan
 Javid yagize akazi keza mu buyobozi bw’igisagara (City)  imbere y’uko aba umushingamateka w’umu-Tory mu 2010
 Uwo yahoze ari umushikiranganji ajejwe imigenderanire yagumye afise ijambo rikomeye i Westminster mu bashingamateka badafise ibiti muri reta kuva aje ubugira kabiri inyuma ya Boris Johnson mu matora y’uguhiganirwa uburongozi mu 2019
 Yarakurikiranye cane poritike za reta mu gihe c’ikiza ca Covid nk’umukuru w’umugwi w’inama nshingamateka ujejwe ibibazo vy’amagara y’abantu
 Ariko hamwe yoramuka asubiye kurondera uburungozi,  n’uko azoba yizeye ko abanyamugambwe bazomubona ukundi ugereranije nu mu myaka itatu iheze, aho yavuze ko kuba yatoye kuguma mw’ishirahamwe rya Buraya mu matora ya kamarampaka yari intambanyi atashobora gusimba
 Umuhungu w’umu Amiral, Hunt yatungishijwe na Hotcourses – urubuga rwa internet yashinze ruhuza abarondera amashure  ya kaminuza bigako n’ibigo bifise ayo mashure
 Umushingamateka wa South West Surrey kuva mu 2005, Hunt yinjiye muri reta mu 2010 nk’umushikiranganji ajejwe imico n’akaranga yongera araba umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y'abantu
 Umushikiranganji ajejwe ikigega muri iki gihe yashimangiye kuba umwizigirwa igihe yashingwa igisata c’incanco mu gihe c’ikiza , hanyuma aronka icizere cinshi mu gikorwa co gutanga incanco mu Bwongereza
 Yavuze ati “ni ko kazi ka mbere gakomeye nkoze mu buzima” - n’ubwo kabaye intango yo kumuduza akaba umushikiranganji ajejwe  amashure
 Kwongerwa guhabwa ikindi giti nk’umushikiranganji ajejwe ikigega aho Rishi Sunak atangiye imihoho ntivyamubujije, ata n’amasaha 24 aheze,  kuja mu mugwi w’abashikiranganji  babwiye Boris Johnson ko hageze ko agenda
 Zahawi yavukiye muri Iraq mu 1967, hanyuma umuryango wiwe uhunga igihe Saddan Hussein yashika ku butegetsi
 Amaze kurangiza amashuri y’ubu enjeniyeri muri chimie (shimi), yashinze kompanyi igurisha Teletubbies imbere y’uko ashinga ikigo c’ugutora kuri internet YouGov
 Yabaye umushingamateka wa Conservative wa Stratford-Upon-Avon mu 2010
 Nk’uwigeze kuba afasha ‘umu-magicien’, Penny Mordaunt azwi nk’umuntu ashika ku bintu mu buryo butangaje, Mu majambo ya poritike, aja yaramaze kuvana “urukwavu mu nkofero” (kuronka ikintu mu buryo butanganje)  mu 2019, igijhe yandika amateka mu kuba umushikiranganji w’Ubwongereza ajejwe kwivuna abansi – ikibanza cari kimukwiye kuko yari amaze kuba umuyobozi mukuru ajejwe ingabo za  gisirikare kuri reta ya David Cameron
 Ariko Madame  Mordaunt ashobora kuba azwi cane kurusha hanze ya Westminster mu kiganiro c’ivyamamare, Splah!, co kuri ITV co kurondera amafaranga yo gufasha mu bikorwa vy’ubugiraneza
 Umushikirangamateka wa Portsmouth North kuva mu 2010, Madame Mordaunt yahoze ari umukuru w’ishami ry’urwaruka mu mugambwe wa Conservative, yarabaye kandi uwujejwe kumenyesha amakuru wa William Hague igihe ariwe yari arongoye umugambwe
 Imbere yo kuja muri reta, yari ajejwe kumenyesha amakuru mu buyobozi bw’igisagara muri Kessington na Chelsea hamwe na Freight Transport Association, niho yashigikira abanyonga ama kamyo mu Bwongereza igihe Ubufaransa bwari bwafashe ibihano
  Umushikiranganji ajejwe kwivuna abansi akaba yahoze ari umusikirikare, n’umuntu ataboneka cane yatanguye kumenyekana kuva Uburusiya buteye Ukraine, igihe Ubwongereza bwatangaza hakiri kare ingingo yo gushigikira Kyiv mu kuyiha ibigwnanisho n’inyigisho
 N’ubwo yari ateye kubiri na Brexit, Wallace niwe yari ajejwe ibikorwa vyo kwiyamamaza vya Boris Johnson ataco vyashitseko mu 2017, imbere y’uko ashimirwa mu guhabwa ikibanza c’umushikiranganji mu 2019
 Yarakoze mu Budagi, Chipre, Belize na Irlande ya  Ruguru aho yatekuruje umugambi wa IRA wo kugaba igitero c’amabombe ku ngabo z’Ubwongereza
 Yabaye kandi umwe mu basikare bakomeye bari mu gikorwa co kurondera ikiziga c’Umuganwakazi  Diana i Paris
  Michael Gov yari mu babonwa nk'abashobora gusubirira Boris Johnon ariko yamaze kumenyesha ko atazoja mw'ihiganwa
 Uwo mushikiranganji  ajejwe kugabanya ubusumbane yari amaze kwitoza kabiri nk’indongozi y’aba-Tory n’umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Mu 2019 yabaye uwa gatatu kuri Boris Johnson na Jeremy Hunt
 Abandi bamaze kumenyesha ko batazohiganwa ni icegera c'umushikiranganji wa mbere Dominic Raab n'uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu Matt Hancock

Boris Johnson yavuze yuko "bibabaje cane kuba ntashoboye guheraheza imigambi myiza n'ivyiyumviro" yari afise mu gihe yatanze imihoho nk'umukuru w'umugambwe uri ku butegetsi mu Bwongereza, Conservative
 Uyu mushikirangani wambere yakirijwe amashi n'impundu vy'umuryango wiwe n'abamufasha mu kazi, igihe yashikiriza ijambo ryo gutanga imihoho ari imbere y'ibiro vyiwe bizwi nka No 10
 Yavuze yuko ikirangaminsi co guhiganirwa gutora uwuzomusubirira kizotangazwa mu ndwi iza
 Uwuzotsinda iryo higanwa niwe azoca yitegurira kuba umushikiranganji wambere mushasha w'Ubwongereza
 Bwana Johnson yahuye n'umufunda w'ibitsure bikomeye vy'abashikiranganji kubera uburongozi bwiwe
 Uwo mufunda watangujwe n'ugutanga imihoho kudasanzwe kw'umushikiranganji ajejwe ubutunzi, Rishi Sunak, hamwe n'uwujejwe amagara y'abantu, Sajid Javid, ku mugoroba wo kuwa kabiri
 Yararinze ibitsure vy'abamusavye bose gutanga imihoho - barimwo n'umushirakiranganji mushasha w'ubutunzi, Nadhim Zahawi, yari ahejeje kugena - ikiringo c'amasaha 48 gushika abonye yuko umugambwe wamukuyeko icizere, atagishoboye kubandanya
 Aho yashikiriza ijambo ari Downing Street (aho akorera kandi akanaba) yavuze yuko yahawe "inshingano zikomeye" mu matora rusangi yo mu 2019, atsinda "ku bwinshi umugambwe wa Conservative utari bwaronke kuva mu 1987"
 "Igituma narwanye bikomeye mu minsi mikeyi iheze ngo mbandanye nshikana inshingano zanje ubwanje, si kubera yuko gusa nabishaka, ni uko numva ari akazi kanje, ari co njejwe, ideni nari ndabafitiye ryo kubashikanira ivyo twabemereye mu 2019"
 Yagize ati "ndicuza kuba ntashoboye guhangana nkatsinda abumva ko ngomba gukinjura", ariko yemera yuko ico umugambwe washaka "cagaragara neza"
 Yavuze kandi ati "muri politike nta n'umwe ari ntayegayezwa", yongerako ati: "Ndashaka yuko mwese mumenya ingene ntewe agahinda no kuba mvuye mu kazi kambere keza kw'isi, ariko nta kundi vyari kugenda"

Ukraine ivuga ko iriko iragira amatohoza ku vyaha bishobora kuba ari ivyo mu ntambara n'ivyo kuvogerwa vyakozwe n'Uburusiya kuva ico gihugu gitewe
 Umushikirizamanza mukuru Iryna Venediktova yabwiye BBC ko yaronse ivyegeranyo biri hagati y'ivyaha vyo mu ntambara 200 na 300 ku musi umwe
 Aremeza ko nyinshi muri izo manza zishobora kuzocibwa abagirizwa batahari, ariko amenyesha ko ari "ikibazo c'ubutungane" kubandanya guca izo manza
 Uburusiya bwateye Ukraine itariki 24 z'ukwezi kwa kabisi
 Burahakana ivyaha vyose vyo mu ntambara bwagirizwa
 Avugana na BBC, Venediktova yagabishije abasirikare b'Uburusiya bishe, bagasinzikariza ubuzima abantu canke bagafata ku nguvu abasivile ko "bategerezwa kumenya ko ari ikibazo c'umwanya gusa kugira bose bashikirizwe ubutungane"
 Yavuze ko n'aho umugwi arongoye uriko urakorera mu turere twose muri Ukraine, utashoboye kugira amatohoza ku vyaha vyose "neza kandi ata nzitizi" kubera kudashobora gushikira abantu bamwe bamwe n'uturere
 Aha bigaragara ko yashaka kuvuga uturere twigaruriwe n'ingabo z'Uburusiya
 Mu kwezi kwa gatanu, Venediktova yavuze ko abantu bakekwako ivyaha 600 bamaze kumenyekana kandi ko imanza 80 zimaze gutangura
 Umusirikare wa mbere w'Umurusiya yaciriwe urubanza muri Ukraine ni Sgt Vadim Shishimarin, yaciriwe urubanza rwo gupfungwa ubuzima bwiwe bwose yagirizwa kwica umusivile mu kwezi kwa gatanu
 Ukraine ivuga ko imaze gutahura ibindi bibanza vyatawemwo abantu ikivunga i Bucha, Borodyanka hamwe no mu bindi bisagara vyegereye umugwa mukuru Kyiv hari higaruriwe n'ingabo z'Uburusiya umwanya muto
 Sentare mpuzamakungu mpanavyaha yavuze ko Ukraine ari "ikibanza c'ubwicanyi", inarungikayo igitigiri kinini c'abafasha mu matohoza kitari bwaboneke muri ico gihugu, gufasha
 Uburusiya bwagumye buhakana ko budatera abasivile
 Ku rubuga rw'intambara, abasirikare ba Ukraine bavuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya ziriko zirategura ibitero ku karere ko mu buseruko ka Donetsk, mu gutera ibibombe ku bisagara vyinshi
 Uburusiya bwarigaruriye akarere ka Luhansk nka kose mu mpera z'indwi iheze, nk'imwe ntumbero yo kugerageza kwigarurira akarere ka Donbas kose
 Mu nkuru zishasha, igisirikare ca Ukraine kivuga ko ingabo zaco ziriko ziraterwa cane ariko ko gushika ubu bashoboye kuzihagarika
 Ababa i Slovyansk, igisagara nkenerwa kiri mu minwe ya Ukraine, basabwe kukivamwo bahungire mu burengero - umusi umwe inyuma y'igitero c'Uburusiya kw'isoko cahitanye abantu benshi
 Hagati aho, prezida wa Ukriane Volodymyr Zelensky, yavuze ati "ibigwanisho birasa kure vya bagenzi bacu b'i Buraya vyatanguye gukora n'inguvu, igitigiri c'abaduteye bahasiga ubuzima kizokwiyongera"

Abakuru b’ibisata vy’Ubwongereza na Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bijejwe igendereza baremeshereje hamwe ikiganiro n’abanyamakuru, ibitari bwigere bibaho, bagabisha ko Ubushinwa bushobora guteza akaga
 Umukuru w’ikigo FBI (kijejwe igendereza muri Amerika) Christopher Wray avuga ko Ubushinwa ari bwo "kaga gakomeye cane ku butunzi n’umutekano vy’igihugu cacu”, kandi bwarivanze no muri poritike, harimwo no mu matora aheruka
 Umukuru wa MI5 (igisata kijejwe igendereza rya gisirikare mu Bwongereza) Ken McCallum avuga ko igisata ciwe congereje incuro zirenga  zibiri imirimo yaco yo kugendererza ibikorwa n’Ubushinwa mu myaka itatu iheze, kandi ko gishobora no gusubira kurenzako izindi ncuro zibiri
 Yongerako y’uko ubu MI5 ikora igendereza rijanye n’ibikorwa vy’umugambwe w’abakomunista mu Bushinwa ku rugero rw’incuro indwi ugereranije no mu 2018
 Wray arongoye FBI agabisha ko mu gihe Ubushinwa bworamuka bwigaruriye Taiwan ku nguvu “bishobora kuba kimwe  mu bintu vyohungabanya ubucuruzi mu buryo isi itarigera ibona”
 Iyi nama ya mbere ibereye ku mugaragaro hagati y’aba bategetsi babiri yabereye ku cicaro ca MI5 kiri mu nyubakwa Thames House ku mugwa mukuru w’Ubwongereza, Londres
 McCallum avuga kandi ko akaga gatewe n’umugambwe w’Abakomunista w’Ubushinwa “kazotuma ibintu bihinduka”, mu gihe Wray na we avuga ko “gakomeye cane” kandi “gahagaritse umutima”
 Wray yagabishije abariko baramwumviriza – harimwo abayobozi nshingwabikorwa b’amashirahamwe y’ubudandaji hamwe n’abategetsi b’amakaminuza  - ko reta y’Ubushinwa yiteguye “kwiba ubuhinga bwanyu” ikoresheje uburyo butandukanye
 Avuga ko iki gihugu co muri Asia ari “akaga gakomeye ku budandaji bwo mu bihugu vy’Uburengero gusumba uko abahinga bakomeye mu vy'ubudandaji bavyibaza”
 Avuga kandi ko Ubushinwa bwarungitse ba maneko nyabwonko (cyber espionage) kugira bakore "ubusuma bwo ku rwego rwo hejuru”, mu gukoresha porogaramu yo kwiba amakuru nini cane gusumba iyo mu bindi bihugu vyose bikomeye bigiye hamwe
 Umukuru wa MI5 avuga ko amakuru y’igendereza ku vyerekeye iterabwoba nyabwonko yahawe ibihugu 37 kandi ko mu kwa gatanu umugambi wo ku rwego rwo hejuru wo guhungabanya ibikorwa vy’ikirere wasambuwe
 McCallum yatanze kandi uturorero dufitaniye isano n’Ubushinwa
 Muri two harimwo umuhinga mu bijanye n’indege yarondewe akemererwa akazi keza
