Hellen yagiye muri Arabia Saudite mu 2019
 Yari yahevye ishure ari mu mwaka wa gatandatu akaba yabona ko inzira yonyene yotuma atera imbere akanafasha n'umuryango wiwe kuva mu bukene kwari ukuja mu bindi bihugu
 Akaryo ko kuja muri Arabia Saudite igihe kaboneka, ntiyazuyajije
 Avuga ko yahora yumva ibintu vyinshi bishikira bamwe mu bakobwa bakora ubuzi bwo mu mazu bagiye mu bihugu bitandukanye vyo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati, ariko we yari afise icizere ko azobirinda vyose kugira ashike ku ndoto yiwe yo kuva mu bukene
 Mu misi adashobora kwibagira harimwo itariki 9 z'ukwezi kwa kabiri mu 2019 aho yinyegeza umwana wiwe w'umuhungu ashaka kugenda muri Arabia Saudite
 Uwo mugore yarumvise umubabaro mwinshi igihe yasiga umwana wiwe afise imyaka ine, ariko ku mutima we yabona ko imyaka ibiri ari mike aravye ico agiye kurondera
 Amaze gushika muri Arabia Saudite, Hellen avuga ko yakiriwe n'umugabo n'umugore bamuhaye akazi ko gukora mu nzu, ubwo nyene baca bamujana muhira iwabo
 Uko uwo mugore abivuga, n'aho yari amaze gukora akazi ko mu nzu muri Kenya  imyaka irenga cumi, yatanguye kugira ikibazo akihashika kubera ururimi bituma batumvikana neza n'umukoresha
 Ikindi ubushuhe bwari bwinshi bukamutera ingorane cane
 Icizere ko ibintu bizogenda neza yarakigumanye, ivyo vyose aravyihanganira, akabifata nk'ibintu bito yiyumviriye icamuzanye
 Uko imisi igenda, ni ko yagenda arabona ko akazi ari kenshi cane, buri musi akazinduka mu gitondo, akaryama mu gicugu, kenshi nk'isaha cumi z'ijoro
 Hellen avuga ko inyuma y'amezi icenda ya mbere akora ako kazi, yiyumvisemwo ko hageze ko asubira muhira - muri Kenya, ariko ikibazo kiba amasezerano bari bafitaniye
 Ukugerageza gutoroka vyaranse, kuko mu masezerano hari handitse ko akorera uwamuhaye akazi imyaka ibiri
 Gufatwa nabi vyaratinze biba ibintu bisanzwe aravyihanganira abandanya akazi
 Hellen avuga ko igihe yatangura akazi bari bavuganye ko bazoza baramuhemba amadolari 250 ku kwezi, angana n'amafaranga akoreshwa muri ico gihugu Riyal  900
 Avuga ko yarungika ama Riyal 500 ku kwezi muhira muri kenya yo gufasha umwana wiwe, yibaza ko ayandi 400 asigaye, umukoresha wiwe ayamubikiye  gushika igihe azosubirira muri Kenya
 Uwo mugore w'imyaka 29 aturuka mu burengero bwa Kenya avuga ko yigumije arakora akazi ataruhuka
 Hellen aribuka ibintu vyamushikiye biteye ubwoba igihe nabuja yava muhira n'abana biwe bagiye kwinezereza nk'uko vyama ku misi mikuru
 Umugabo w'uwo mugore yaciye aza ikitaraganya aca arinjira yugara imiryango yose
 Yaciye amusaba kumutekera ikawa , mu gihe ataranaheza, yaciye amusimbirako, barazunguturana nk'iminota mirongo itatu, ashaka kumufata ku nguvu
 Hellen yarashatse gutabaza ariko yarabona ko bidashoboka kuko iyo nzu yari nini ku buryo atawari kumwumva
 Agahengwe yakaronse ari uko itelefone yo mu nzu ihamagaye hanyuma aca aramurekura gato, aca aronka akaryo ko kwiruka yiyugaranira mu bwogero gushika umugore w'uwo mugabo agaruke
 Agira ati:"Ivyo vyantumye nipfuza gutaha muhira uko bigenda kose
 Naratinye kugira uwo mbwira ivyanshikiye
 Ico natinya kinini n'uko atawari kuvyemera kandi ko ari jewe nari kwagirizwa amakosa
 Naciye mfata ingingo yo kurondera uwanzanye
" Kuva ico gihe, Hellen yaciye atangura kugerageza guhamagara muhira, kugira arabe ko ubutumwa bwoshikira abamutwayeyo bo muri Kenya, ko wewe ata mahoro afise ko yipfuza gutaha bivanye no kubangamirwa k'ubuzima bwiwe
 Urugamba rwo gusubira muri Kenya rwatanguye igihe abamurondereye akazi ku ruhande rwa Arabia Saudite batangura kuganira n'umukoresha wiwe, bamusaba ko yubahiriza amasezerano bafitaniye yari yimirije kurangira inyuma y'imyaka ibiri
 Hellen avuga ko atari bwigere yubahuka kuvuga ko yahatswe gufatwa ku nguvu kubera ubwoba
 Yongerako ko, icari kimuraje ishinga gusumba ico gihe, kwari gutahuka
 Itariki 6 z'ukwezi kwa gatanu uyu mwaka, Hellen yavyuwe hakiri kare cane n'umukoresha wiwe, abwirwa ko atekera agataha muri Kenya
 Yabwiwe ko itike y'indege yamaze kugurwa, ntiyahabwa n'akanya ko kwitegura
 Icamubabaje cane uretse ibibi yakorewe, n'uko mu mahera y'ama Riyal ibihumbi cumi na bitatu umukoresha wiwe yagiye aramubikira yacaguka ku mushahara, umukoresha wiwe yamurishe igice kingana na Riyal 6500
 Ariko Hellen yarahimbawe n'uko yagarutse afise amagara meza
 Avuga ko, ikibazo nyamukuru abakobwa bakunze kuja gukora akazi ko mu nzu mu bihugu vy'abarabu, ni kutamenya ingene bokwifata igihe bashikiwe n'ingorane, na cane cane ko batumva ururimi hamwe n'imico n'imigenzo
 Ica kabiri, benshi mu bakoresha bafata abakozi nka Hellen nk'abaja, ivyo bikavana n'amahera menshi bariha ababajana muri ivyo bihugu babavanye mu bihugu bitandukanye vya Afrika no muri Aziya 
 Ubu Hellen yatanguje akazi ko kugurisha indagara mu micungararo ya Nairobi kandi avuga ko make aronka amukwiye

Abashakashatsi bo muri Finlande bakoze bateri ya mbere kw’isi ikoresha umusenyi ishobora kubika inguvu zidakomotse ku bitoro biva mu kuzimu mu kiringo c’amezi menshi mu gihe kimwe
 Abayikoze bavuga ko ivyo bishobora kuba inyishu ku kibazo co kuronka inguvu umwaka wose, ingorane zikomeye ku masoko ntanganguvu adakomoka ku bitoro vyimbwa mu kuzimu
 Hakoreshejwe umusenyi w’intete nto, iyo bateri ica ishushwa n’inguvu zizimbutse zivuye ku mishwarara y’izuba canke ku muyaga
 Uwo musenyi uca ubika ubwo bushuhe gushika ku  rugero rwa Celcius 500, hanyuma igashobora gususurutsa amazu mu gihe c’imbeho nyinshi (hiver/winter) aho ibiciro vy’inguvu biba vyaduze cane
 Gaz nyinshi Finlande  ikoresha iyivana mu Burusiya, ubu rero intambara ya Ukraine yatumye kwibaza ahova ayandi masoko ntanganguvu  bisubira guhabwa ikibanza gikomeye
 Amakenga ku bitanga ubushuhe n’amatara, na cane cane ubu himirije igihe kirekire kandi c’imbeho nyinshi muri Finlande   biraraje ishinga abanyeporitike co kimwe n’abanyagihugu
 Ariko ubu habonetse ubuhinga bushobora kugabanya imwe muri iyo myitwarariko
 Igikomeye muri ubwo buhinga bushasha ni igiki? Hafi amatoni 100 y’umusenyi  ukoreshwa mu kwubaka, wuzuye ikigega gisa n’isafuriya giteretse ngaho
 Izo ntete z’umusenyi zishobora kuba ari inzira yoroshe kandi isaba uburyo buke yo kubika inguvu zizokoreshwa igihe zizoba zikenewe cane
 Kubera ihindagurika ry’ibihe ubu naho hongeyeko  ibicio vy’ibitoro bikomoka mu kuzimu biguma vyiyongera, ubu hashizwe  uburyo bwinshi mu kurondera ahova inguvu ziturutse ku masoko yisubiriza
 Mu gihe   umuyagankuba uturutse ku buhinga bushasha bw’imishwarara y’izuba n’umuyaga ushobora gufatanywa n‘uwari usanzwe ukoreshwa mu gihugu, ayo masoko mashasha yongeweko azanana n’ibindi bibazo
 Kimwe mu bibazo bikomeye cane ni ukumenya ingene amatara ashobora kuguma yaka igihe izuba ritatse canke ata muyaga uhari
 Kwongera ayandi masoko ntanganguvu yisubiriza ku rufatane rw’umuyagankuba bisigura ko utegerezwa gusubiramwo itunganywa  neza ry’ingene isoko ryose ritanga umwimbu kugira urufatane rugume rukora neza mu bihe vyose, kuko inguvu z’umurengera canke inguvu zidahagije zishobora gutuma ruhungabana
 Inyishu iza ubwa mbere muri ico kibazo ni amabateri manini ashobora kubika akanatanga inguvu igihe urufatane rwose ruzoba rusigaye rukoresha amasoko yisubiriza kurusha ayava ku bitoro bikomoka mu kuzimu
 Gushika ubu, amabateri menshi akozwe muri lithium, arazimvye kandi akaba manini manini cane , kandi akaba hari inguvu atarenza
 Ariko mu gisagara ca Kankaanpää, umugwi w’aba injeniyeri b’abanya-Finlande barangije kwubaka bateri ya mbere yo gushira kw’isoko ikozwe mu musenyi bibaza ko igiye gutanga inyishu yo kubika inguvu mu buryo bworoshe
 Umuyagankuba uzimbutse ushusha umusenyi gushika ku bushuhe bwa dogere (degre)  Celsius  500
 Bituma haba umwuka ushushe ugaca utembera muri uwo musenyi hakoreshwe ikindi cuma c’uguhanahana ubushuhe
 Umusenyi n’inzira yoroshe yo kubika ubushuhe kandi utakaza bike cane ku gihe kirekire
 Abakoze iyo bateri bavuga ko umusenyi ushobora kumara amezi menshi ushushe ku ma dogere Celsius 500
 Iyo rero ibiciro vy’inguvu biduze cane, iyo bateri ica irekura uwo mwukwa ushushe nawo ugashusha amazi nayo agaca asunikwa mu miringoti ija mu mazu, mu biro mbere no mu kizunga co kwogamwo (piscine/swimming pool)
  Iciyumviro ca bateri y’umusenyi catanguriye ku ruganda  rusya ibiti  bikorwamwo impapuro mu gisagara ca Tampere
 Igisigaye kumenya ni uko ubwo buhinga bushobora gutunganywa kugira buzane ubudasa -ikindi ni ukumenya niba abakoze ubwo buhinga bashobora no guhingura umuyagankuba  nk’uko baronka ubushuhe
 Hageze ku muyagankuba, ubwo buhinga ntibusubira gukora neza
 Ariko no gushobora kubika nk’ubushuhe inguvu zidaturutse ku bitoro bikomoka mu kuzimu navyo ni inkuru nziza muri ico gisata aho ubushuhe bukoreshwa ku vyo kurya,  mu guhingura impuzu  n’imiti buva mu gucana ibitoro bikomoka mu kuzimu
 Ubwo buhinga bwa bateri zikozwe mu musenyi hari n‘ibindi bigo biriko birabwiga nko muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika
 Ariko abo muri Finlande babaye abambere bakoze iyo bateri gushika ubu ikora neza, nk’uko bivugwa n’umugabo yabishizemwo umutahe
 Pekka Passi, umuyobozi w’uruganda rw’inguvu rwa  Vatajankoski ati: “Biroroshe cane, ariko twarakunze cane ico ciyumviro co kugerageza ikintu gishasha, kuba aba mbere kw’isi bakoze ikintu nk’iki
” “Ushatse wovuga ko ari nk’ugusara, ariko nibaza ko bizogenda neza cane
”
