Umuntu yitwaje inkoho yateye inyubakwa y’idandarizo (centre commercial/shopping mall) yica abantu batatu akomeretsa n’abandi, nk’uko igipolisi kibitangaza
 Umugabo w’imyaka 22 niwe yahagaritswe yagirizwa ko ari we yakoze iki gitero cabereye mu nyubakwa y’idandarizo ya Field mu bumanuko bw’umugwa mukuru Copenhagen
 Umukuru w’igipolisi avuga ko imvo z’iki gitero zitaramenyekana ariko akaba adashira ku ruhande ko coba ari ic’iterabwoba
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Mette Frederiksen avuga ko Danemark yakozweko igitero c’ubugome
 Mu butumwa bwo guhoza yarungikiye imiryango yabuze ababo, umupfasoni Frederiksen yavuze ko ashaka gutera intege abanya-Danemark ko bofatana mu nda bagafashanya muri iki gihe c’umubabaro
 Ati: "Danemark yakozweko igitero c’ubugome mw’ijoro ryo ku wa Mungu
 Hari abatari bake bishwe abandi benshi bakomeretse
 Imiryango y’intungane yariko ifungura, iyindi isuma
 Abana, imiyabaga n’abakuze”
 Yongerako ati: "Umugwa mukuru wacu mwiza kandi usanzwe utekanye wahindutse mu kanya isase”
 Umuryango w’umwamikazi wa Danemark wifatanije n’umubabaro mwinshi “n’abakozweko iki gitero, incuti zabo n’abo bose cagizeko ingaruka”
 Mw’itangazo basohoreye hamwe, umwamikazi Margrethe, igikomangoma Frederik n’igikomangomakazi Mary banditse bati: "Ntituramenya neza ivyononekariye muri aka kaga, ariko biraboneka ko hari benshi bahasize ubuzima mbere n’abandi batari bake bakomeretse”
 Uwikekwa ko ari we yakoze iki gitero yari afise inkoho n’amasasu igihe yahagarikwa, nk’uko bivugwa n’igipolisi
 Uyu yikekwa ko yakoze igitero, igipolisi kivuga ko ari umunye-Danemark”, ararengutswa imbere y’umucamanza kuri uno wa mbere
 Igipolisi kivuga ko ata kimenyetso kihari c’uko hari abandi bari kumwe, kinasaba abafise amaduka kubungabunga amavidewo bashobora kuba bafise
 Iyi nyubakwa ifise amaduka n’amazu y’uburiro arenga 140
 Iyi nyubakwa y’amagorofa menshi iri ku nkengera za  Copenhagen, ku kabarabara neza na neza kinjira hagati mu gisagara
 Ababibonye bavuga ko abari muri ino nyubakwa batekewe n’ubwoba igihe uyu yakoze iki gitero yatsa umuriro
 Umwe muri bo, azwi kw’izina rya Isabelle, yabwiye ibinyamakuru vya Danemark ati: "Twagiye twumva amasasu
 Nibaza ko numvise amasasu cumi duca twiruka duhunga, twisanga turi mu kazu ka surwumwe, turundanirayo, mu kumba gato, turi hafi abantu 11
 Igiteramo c’umuririmvyi w’umwongereza Harry Styles cari gitegekanijwe hafi y’aho caciye gihagarikwa
 Mu butumwa yacishije kuri Snapchat, Styles avuga ati: "Umurwi wanje na jewe nyene turasabira aba bantu bahuye n’iki gitero co mu nyubakwa y’idandarizo i Copenhagen
 Ndababaye cane
 H arabakunda”
 Inyuma y’ico gitero kandi, umuryango w’umwamikazi watangaje ko ihuriro ryo kwivuna umusase ryari riteguwe n’igikomangoma Frederik ryahagaze
 Ryari ihuriro ryo kwigina akaryo Danemark yahawe ko kwakira ibice bitatu vy’ihiganwa ry’amakinga Tour de France
 Abategetsi batari bake b’ibihugu bibanyi berekanye umubabaro wabo bongera bahoza imirango yahaburiye ababo n’iyakozweko n’iki gitero
 Danemark yaheruka kubona igitero gikomeye mu 2015, aho abantu babiri bishwe, abapolisi batandatu nabo barakomereka mu gitero cabereye ku nzu ndangamuco no kw’isinagoga y’i Copenhagen
 Uwakoze iki gitero yahavuye apfa mu kurasana kwabaye hagati ya we n’abapolisi

Igisirikare ca Ukraine cahavuye cemeza ko igisagara ca Lysychansk kiri mu buseruko cafashwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya
 Ibiro bikuru vy’igisirikare ca Ukraine vyatangaje biti: "Inyuma y’intambara zikomeye i Lysychansk, vyabaye ngombwa ko ingabo za Ukraine ziva ku birindiro vyazo”
 Imbere y’aha, umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi w’Uburusiya Sergei Shoigu yari yamaze gutangaza ko ingabo ziwe zafashe Lysychansk kandi ko ubu zigaruriye intara yose ya Luhansk
 Ingabo za Ukraine zahavuye zirengerwa
 Ibiro bikuru vy’igisirikare bivuga ko "mu ntumbero yo kuzigama ubuzima bw’abarwanira Ukraine, hafashwe ingingo yo kuzivanayo”
 Bivuga ko Abarusiya babarushije inguvu mu nzira nyinshi harimwo ibirwanisho vya rutura, indege, abasirikare n’ibindi
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zizotegerezwa gusubira muri Lysychansk kubera ubuhinga bwazo “n’ibindi birwanisho vya none biriko birongerezwa”
 Imbere y’aha, umukuru wa Repubulika ya Chechnya/ Tchétchénie, Ramzan Kadyrov, yari yasohoye ireresi isa n’iyerekana abarwanyi ba Chechnya  bari hagati mu gisagara ca Lysychansk
 Hirya mu burengero, igisagara ca Slovyansk  kiri mu minwe ya Ukraine cacucagiwe amabombe, aho abantu n’imiburiburi batandatu bahasize ubuzima
 Intara ya Donetsk, iri kumwe na Luhansk, igize akarere kagizwe n’amahinguriro ya Donbas
 Imbere gato y’uko atanguza intambara, Perezida  Vladimir Putin yemeje Luhansk na Donetsk k’intara zigenga ziyonkoye kuri Ukraine
 Ingabo zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya zatanguje intambara mu 2014
 Haraciye indwi irenga ingabo z’Uburusiya zigaruriye Severodonetsk, igisagara cacitse umunyota inyuma y’amayinga atari make camaze giterwa amabombe n’Uburusiya
 Slovyansk na Kramatorsk ni vyo bisagara bibiri mu ntara ya Donetsk bikiri mu minwe y’ingabo za Ukraine
 Ibibombe vyacucagiwe i Slovyansk ejo ku wa Mungu vyatumye haduka imiriro mu duce 15, nk’uko umukuru Vadym Lyakh abivuga, mbere videwo yerekana imyotsi myinshi hejuru y’ico gisagara
 Avuga ko ari co gitero c’amabombe gikomeye giheruka
 Amashusho yacishijwe ku rubuga rwa Twitter yerekana ibiturika bikomeye biboneka kure -  i Slovyansk nk’uko indondasanamu ibisigura
 Yacishijweko na  Iuliia Mendel yahoze ari umuvugizi wa Perezida Zelensky
 BBC ntiyashoboye guhinyuza ingene ibintu bimeze i Slovyansk

Igisirikare muri Uganda cabeshuje inkuru z’uko ico gihugu kriko kiragerageza guhungabanya Ethiopia mu guha inyigisho za gisisirikare no gushigikira umuhari wa  Tigray People’s Liberation Front, TPLF, uriko uragwanya reta ya Ethiopia kuva mu 2020
 Izo nkuru ziboneka nk’izatanguye kuja ahabona mu kwezi kwa gatanu ku mbuga hwaniro za Ethiopia
 Umuvugizi w’igisirikare ca Uganda Brigadier Felix Kulayigye yanditse kuri Twitter ku wa Mungu ko ibivugwa ko Uganda iriko iragerageza guhungabanya Ethiopia bitagira ishingiro na gato
 Inkuru y’ido n’ido yasohotse ku ndwi iheze ku rubuga rwo muri Nouvelle Zelande (New Zealand) hamwe n’amazina y’abasirikare n’abandi bajejwe umutekano bakuru bavugwa ko ari bo bahagarariye ico gikowa muri district ya Masaka
 Iyo nyandiko ivuga ko abasirikare 4000 b’aba-Tigray bari guhabwa ivyo vyigwa mu bibanza bine bitandukanye
 Iyo nkuru ivuga kandi ko ico gikorwa co kwigisha gishigikiwe na reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika na Misiri
 Umwe mu bantu bakomeye avugwa muri iyo nkuru n’umuhungu w’umukuru w’igihugu ca Uganda, jenerari Muhoozi Kainerugaba, yanditse kuri twitter ko ashigikiye ingabo za Tigray, abita "abavukanyi" mu 2021
 Ntibizwi niba iyo nyandiko ari iyo ukuri, kandi urwo rubuga rwo muri Nouvelle Zelande rwavuze ko rutashoboye guhinyuza isoko ryarwo canke ibirimwo
 Ariko harimwo bimwe bimwe bidahuye n'ukuri
 Haravugwamwo James Kabarebe nk'uwabaye umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi wa Uganda, ariko ico gihugu nta mushikiranganji yitwa gutyo cigeze kigira muri ico kibanza
 Brigadier Kulayigye yanditse kandi kuri twitter ko ugufashanya kuvugwa hagati ya Uganda na Sudan y'Epfo muri ico gikorwa atari ukuri
 Avuga ko uwuhagarariye Uganda muri Sudan y'Epfo, avugwa mu guhuza bimwe muri ico gikorwa, atigeze abonana n'umujenerari wo muri Sudan y'Epfo avugwa muri iyo nkuru
 Ariko igihugu ca Uganda kirafise kahise ko kugira uruhara mu ntambara zo mu karere
 Ubu ingabo zabwo ziri mu buseruko bwa Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo no muri Somalia, kandi caragize uruhara mu gutabara reta ya Sudan y’Epfo igihe intambara yaduka muri ico gihugu mu 2013

Igipolisi ca Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika cashize ahabona videwo y’ingene ciruka ku muntu i Akron, Ohio, ivyagiye kurangira umugabo w’umwirabure arashwe amasasu arenga 60 n’abapolisi bariko baramuhiga
 Igipolisi cemeza ko Jayland Walker w’imyaka 25 ari we yatanguye kurasa, bituma abapolisi bibaza ko batewe igihe bamuhagarika mw’ijoro ryo ku wa 27 ruheshi
 Walker nta nkoho yari afise igihe yava mu modoka yiruka, ariko igipolisi kivuga ko casanze inkoho ntoya (pistolet) mu modoka
 Igihe hari hatanguye imyiyerekano, umukuru w’igisagara ca Akron yasavye ababa muri ako karere kwihangana
 Iyo videwo imaze gusohoka ejo ku wa Mungu, Daniel Horrigan yavuze ati: "Iyi videwo ni incamugongo, iragoye kwihanganira”
 Umushikirizamanza mukuru muri iyo ntara Dave Yost yemereye abanyagihugu ko Ibiro vya Ohio bijejwe gukurikirana ivyaha bizokora “amatohoza ataho yegamiye kandi yimbitse” mu gihe igipolisi ca Akron kiriko kirakora amatohoza ku ruhande rwaco, kugira kirabe nimba abapolisi barahonyanze amabwirizwa ngenderwako
 Abapolisi umunani bamurashe, indwi muri bo bakaba ari abazungu umwe aka ari we ari umwirabure, bategetswe kuja mu karuhuko ariko bakazohembwa umushahara wabo
 Umushingwamanza umwe w’umuryango wa Walker avuga ko aba bapolisi babandanije barasa n’igiye yari aryamye hasi
 Derrick Johnson, umukuru w’ishirahamwe riharanira agateka k’abatari abazungu (National Association for the Advancement of Colored People), avuga ko urupfu rwa Walker ari Ubwicanyi
 Imbonankubone”
 Imodoka ya Jayland Walker yahagaritswe ku wa mbere igenekerezo rya 27 Ruheshi (6) isaha 00:30 mu bikorwa bisanzwe vyo kugenzura uruja n’uruza rw’amamodoka
 Umukuru w’igipolisi ca Akron, Steve Mylett, asubirwamwo n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru Associated Press, aho avuga ko humvikanye urusasu mu modoka kandi ko kamera igenzura uruja n’uruza yafashe amashusho
 Kamera zambarwa n’abapolisi zerekana umuntu ava mu modoka yiruka atera aja ku gituro c’amamodoka, asiganwa n’abapolisi mu kiringo c’imisegonda cumi imbere y’uko bamurasa
 Igipolisi kivuga ko umwe mu bapolisi yagerageje gukoresha ya nkoho yo gukongataza, ariko biba ivy’ubusa
 Hampande y’iyi nkoho ntoya yatowe ifise igikono cuzuye amasasu ku ntebe imwe muri iyo modoka, ikirombora c’urusasu rw’iyi nkoho rwaratowe hafi, nk’uko igipolisi kibivuga
 Iyo reresi imaze gusohoka, abanu baciye biha amabarabara mu myiyerekano ituje muri Akron baca bakoranira imbere y’ibiro vy’ubucamanza vy’ico gisagara
 Umushingwamanza w’umuryango wa Bobby DiCello avuga ko abapolisi barashe Walker n’igihe yari aryamye kandi ko bamuboshe n’amapingu imbere ‘yuko bamuha ubufasha bwa mbere
 Mw’itangazo bahaye ikinyamakuru BCS News, umuryango wa Walker uvuga uti: “Ishavu ni ryiza
 Ishavu riratahuritse
 Imigumuko si uko
