Ubwongereza bwatangaje amasezerano n'igihugu ca Nigeria ajanye no gutorera inyishu ikibazo c'abimukira badakurikije amategeko
 Mu butumwa yashize kuri twitter, umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza ajejwe intawo yo hagati mu gihugu, Priti Patel, yavuze yuko "aya masezerano ngirakamaro cane na Nigeria azoshira ingoga mu kwirukana inkozi z'ikibi ruhasha z'abanyamahanga"
 Gutangaza aya masezerano kw'ejo kuwa kane kwaje haciye amasaha makeyi hirukanywe abanye-Nigeria bashika cumi mu bijanye no kurenga ku mategeko agenga abimukira
 BBC ntibazwa ibivuye ku zindi mbuga Abaharanira agateka k'abahuza ibitsina n'abo babisangiye hamwe n'abiyumva ko ari ab'igitsina batavukanye (LGBTQ+), bari berekanye impungenge batewe n'abo muri uwo mugwi birukanywe, bari basavye ubuhungiro mu Bwongereza
 Abantu barashobora kwirukanwa mu Bwongereza iyo atari abenegihugu babwo kandi bagiriwe n'icaha c'ubugizi bwa nabi
 Mu ntango za kuno kwezi sentare ya Buraya y'agateka ka zina muntu yarahagaitse indege yambere yagomba gutwara impunzi mu Rwanda
 Urwo rugendo rw'indege rwari mu mugambi wiswe Rwanda asylum plan, watangajwe na leta y'Ubwongereza mu kwezi kwa kane, wo guha zimwe mu mpunzi itike y'indege y'ubutagaruka yo kuja kwaka ubuhungiro mu Rwanda
