Ukraine irishimira intsinzi ikomeye inyuma y’aho Uburusiya bukuriye ingabo zabwo mw’izinga ryitwa Snake Island (Izinga ry’Inzoka), zari zigaruriye ku musi wa mbere nyene zitangura igitero
 Rishobora kuba ari akantu gato, ariko iri zinga ry’urutare rifise uruhara rukomeye muri ino ntambara y’Uburusiya muri Ukraine – aha wokwibuka inkuru y’ingabo za Ukraine kuri rino zinga zibwira n’agasuzuguro ubwato bw’intambara bw’Uburusiya ngo “vaho” – igihe bwazisaba kwishikana
 Ubu, inyuma y’amezi arenga ane Ukraine itera amabombe y’urutavanako, ingabo z’Uburusiya zahevye iri zinga Snake Island, rizwi nk’izinga rya Zmiinyi muri Ukraine
 Iri zinga ry’urutare riri ku birometero 35 uvuye ku nkengera y’inyanja muri Ukraine – intera ntoya ishobora gushikirwa n’ibisasu vya misire, vya muzinga n’ibitero vya za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) bivuye ku butaka
 Ingabo za Ukraine niko zakora, ibitero bikomeye kuri iri zinga hamwe no ku bwato ubwo ari bwo bwose buhirahiriye ngo bwegere
 Uburusiya bwobwo buvuga ko bwavuye kuri ico kirindiro “ku gatima keza” kugira ngo bwerekane ko ata ntumbero bufise yo kuzibira ishorwa ry’intete, ariko Ukraine yoyo iriyamiriza ibi, na rirya Moscou ibandanya icucagira ibisasu ububiko bw’intete
 Iri zinga Snake Island ni akarere kari ahantu ngirakamaro, hakaba hari haciye amezi atari make harangwa intambara
 Iri zinga ry’urutare rito cane riri mu buraruko bushira uburengero  bw’Inyanja Yirabura (Mer Noire/Black Sea) ryari ryafashwe n’Uburusiya ku musi wa mbere w’igitero cabwo kuri Ukraine, kandi ryagize uruhara rudasanzwe muri ino ntambra kuva ico gihe
 Iri zinga riroroshe guterwa uciye ku mpande zose, mu kirere no mu mazi, mu gihe ikirindiro gito cari kiricungereye – ubwa mbere cari ic’abanya-Ukraine hanyuma ic’Abarusiya – abahinga ba gisirikare bakaba barifata nk’akarere kirebanga, kadashobora gukingirwa
 Mu kwa kane, inguvu z’Uburusiya zo kwivuna ibitero vy’indege mu buraruko bushira uburengero bw’inyanja Yirabura zaragabanutse cane igihe bwa bwato bw’intambara Moskva butwarwa
 Kremlin yagumye igerageza kuraba ingene yogarukana ibirwanisho vyo guhangana n’ibitero vy’indege n’ibindi vyo kurwana intambara za elektroniki kuri iri zinga
 Ariko vyabaye ivy’ubusa ku Burusiya, kuricungera biranka kubera ryari kure y’ibirindiro bikuru bikuru vyo mu Nyanja yirabura
 Mu bitero vyose vyayo, Ukraine nta mato menshi ifise, ari co gituma itashoboye gutwara ingabo zayo kuri iri zinga
 Umuhinga wa gisirikare w’umunya-Ukraine Oleh Zhdanov avuga ko gushinga ikirindiro c’ingabo kuri iri zinga ataco bimaze ku mpande zompi kuko vyoroshe guterwa
 Zhdanov abona ko ahubwo igikenewe ari ukugira ubushobozi bwo gutera ikintu ico ri co cose cokwegera iri zinga
 Ibi bishobora guha ubushobozi Ukraine bwo gukingira ikivuko cayo kinini gusumba ibindi vyose ku Nyanja Yirabura, hamwe no mu gace kose k’uburaruko bushira uburengero bw’inyanja Yirabura
 Uburusiya ubu buragenzura akarere katari gato ka Ukraine ku nkengera y’Inyanja Yirabura, hamwe n’ikigwa ca Crimea be n’inyanja yose ya Azov
 Mu kwigarurira iri zinga vyatumye Odesa yugaranwa burundu, ibisigura ko bitashoboka ko Ukraine ishora intete zayo hanze
 Vyasigura kandi ko inkengera y’Inyanja Yirabura yashobora guterwa, abahinga ba gisirikare i Kyiv bakaba berekanye ubwoba bari bafise ko Uburusiya bushobora kuhashinga ikirindiro c’ibirwanisho birasa kure, nk’ibitera za misire zo mu bwoko bwa S-400
 Uravye kw’isanamu, biboneka kandi ko Uburusiya kwigarurira iri zinga vyari bibangamiye umutekano wa Roumanie, umunywanyi wa OTAN/NATO – haba ku kivuko cayo ca Constanta  canke mu ngendo zo mu mazi y’uruzi Danube
 Uretse ko iri zinga riri ahantu hakomeye cane, ni akarere gatunze igitoro hamwe na gaze
 Iyi si intsinzi ikomeye kuri Ukraine, ariko ni intambwe ikomeye
 Ku Burusiya, ni uruhombo ku rugamba rwabwo kandi ni ugutsindwa mu buryo buteye isoni
 Ariko ibi ntibishobora gutuma intambara ihindura isura
 Uburusiya ubu burajwe ishinga no kwigarurira akarere kose ka Donbas kari mu buseruko bwa Ukraine be no kugumana uturere bwigaruriye igihe butangura intambara
 Izinga Snake Island rishobora kuba ari ikibanza gikomye cane mu Nyanja yirabura kandi hakaba n’ahantu heza ho gushinga ibirwanisho bikomeye birasa ibisasu vya misire, ariko ni akarere gato cane k’urutare
 N’aho Abarusiya bahirukanywe, ikibazo nyamukuru ni ukumenya nimba Ukraine ishobora gusubira gushora intete hanze kugira ngo inagure ubutunzi bwayo bwishwe n’intambara
 Ata mato afise ubushobozi ifise, hari igihamana gito, na rirya amato y’intambara y’Uburusiya ari yo yiganje mu Nyanja Yirabura
 Andrew Wilson, umwigisha kw’ishure kaminuza rya Londres ku bijanye n’ibibazo vya Ukraine, avuga ati: "Mu bisanzwe hari ibintu cumi bikenewe kugira ngo ushobore gushora hanze izi ntete ata ngorane, hamaze kuba iki kimwe gusa”
 Ukraine yamiriye kure ibisabwa n’Uburusiya ko bwoherekeza amato y’intete avuye i Odesa kuko bisaba ko ibisasu vya mine hanze y’ikivuko bibanza gutegurwa
 Turukiya iriko irakora uko ishoboye mu guhuza impande zompi kugira bashike ku masezerano ariko ibi bisa n’ibikiri kure nk’ukwezi
 Indwi nkeya ziri imbere zifatwa ko ari ikiringo gikomeye cane ku rudandazwa rwo hanze rwa Ukraine – kubera isarura ryimirije ritangura muri kuno kw’indwi

ONU ivuga ko inyeshamba zarashe ibisasu bitatu vya rokete mu kigo cayo mu buseruko bwa Republika ya Demokrasi ya Congo
 Nta makuru aramenyekana y'ivyoba vyononekaye muri ico gitero cagirijwe umugwi wa M23
 Umuvugizi wa ONU yavuze yuko ibisasu bibiri vyaguye hafi y'ibirindiro vy'abasirikare bayo bahagarariye amahoro mu karere ka Kibindi muri Kivu ya ruguru
 Uruhagarara ruracari rwose mu buseruko bw'ico gihugu mu gihe inyeshamba zibandanya kugaba ibitero ku basirikare ba leta
 Kuwa gatatu umwe mu bakozi ba ONU bo ku rwego rwo hejuru yabwiye akanama kayo kajejwe umutekano yuko abarwanyi ba M23 bitwara nk'igisikare ceruye, hamwe n'ubushobozi bwo kunesha ingabo za ONU
 Hagati aho intumwa idasanzwe ya ONU muri Congo yasavye ko haba, ubu bwa vuba kandi ata kirinze gusabwa, kwaka ibirwanisho imigwi yose yitwaje ibirwanisho muri ico gihugu, ibangamiye umutekano w'akarere k'ibiyaga binini
 Umugwi M23 warongereje ibitero mu buseruko bwa Republika ya Demokrasi ya Congo, unigarurira imiji ikomeye
 Warakuwe mu biganiro vy'amahoro na reta ya Congo biriko birabera mu gihugu ca Kenya
 Abantu barenga imihumbi 170 baramaze guta izabo kuva aho hatanguriye imirwano hagati y'abasirikare ba leta ya Congo n'inyeshamba za M23 mu ntango z'ukwezi kwa kane
 Muri kuno kwezi ishirahamwe ry'ubuseruko bwa Afrika ryafashe ingingo yo kurungika abasirikare muri Congo gufasha leta y'ico gihugu kugarukana amahoro
 BBC iracariko iragerageza kumanye ico M23 ivuga kuri ibi vyagiriji vy'igitero  ku basirikare ba ONU

Leta ya Ethiopia ivuga yuko abantu amajana atatu na mirongo itatu n'umunani bishwe mu ntango za kuno kwezi
 Ni bwo bwicanyi bwa mbere bubi bushingiye ku moko butaheruka muri ico gihugu mu kiringo c'imyaka myinshi
 Vyari vyavuzwe mbere yuko abantu bashika n'imiburiburi amajana abiri na mirongo itanu, bagizwe ahanini n'abo mu bwoko bw'aba-Amhara, biciwe mu gitero mu ntara ya Oromia
 Umuvugizi wo mu biro vy'umushikiranganji wa mbere yavuze yuko igipolisi kikiriko kirakora amatohoza
 Leta yanse ivyasabwe - na ONU irimwo mu babisaba - vy'uko hakorwa itohoza ryigenga kuri ubwo bwicanyi
 Umugwi witwaje ibirwanisho uzwi nka Oromia Liberation Army waragirijwe kugaba ico gitero ariko warabihakanye
 Mu myaka ibiri iheze, iyindi ntara ya Tigrinya nayo yarabayemwo imirwano ikomeye hagati y'abarwanyi b'umuhari TPLF wo muri ako karere n'abasirikare ba leta
 Naho ubu hasa n'ahari agahengwe, umutekano nturahagaruka neza kandi iyo mirwano yasizemwo ubuzima ibihumbi vy'abantu abandi benshi barahunga

Ishirahamwe rijejwe impunzi HCR riremera ko hakiri ibibazo kugira abarundi bahawe ubwenegihugu bwa Tanzania inyuma yo kuba impunzi muri ico gihugu babeho koko nk’abenegihugu buzuye
 Muri abo barundi bashika 162
156 hari abamaze imyaka irenga 14 barahawe ubwenegihugu bwa Tanzania
 Ariko bavuga ko gushika n’uyu munsi benshi bakibayeho nk’impunzi mu makambi ya Ulyankuru, Katumba na Mishamo
 Babibwiye BBC Gahuzamiryango mu kwezi kwa kane uyu mwaka igihe bahimbaza  imyaka 50 yari iheze babayeho mu mahoro kuva bahunze mu 1972
 Mu nyishu ngufi yanditse icegera c’uwuserukira HCR muri Tanzania, George Kuchio, yahaye BBC Gahuzamiryango - yari yifuje kumenya ico iryo shami rya ONU ribivugako kuva ico gihe - avuga ati: “Haracari ibibazo bituma hataboneka inyungu zose zijanye n’uguhabwa ubwenegihugu, nko ku bana bavutse igihe ama dosiye yari akiriko arigwa canke abungururije icemezo ca mbere co  kwimwa ubwenegihugu”
 Kuchio abandanya avuga ko HRC idahengeshanya kuvugana n’abategetsi ba Tanzania kuri ico kibazo kandi ko kiri mu bibazo bashira imbere kugira gitore inyishu
 Abo barundi bahoze ari impunzi bavuga ko batigeze baronswa uburyo bari baremerewe bwo kugura amatongo kugira bubake amazu bongere  barangure imirimo ya minsi yose nk’abandi banye-Tanzania
 N’ubutegetsi bw’igihugu nta matongo bwigeze bubemerera
 HCR ivuga ko muri kahise yarondeye ingene abo bantu bava mu makambi babamwo kugira baje kubana n’abandi banyagihugu ariko ko ico kibazo kikiriko kirigwa n’abategetsi ba Tanzania
 Abarundi barenga 160
000 bahawe ubwenegihugu muri Tanzania bari mu bari barahungiye muri ico gihugu mu 1972
 Ariko n’ubu ico gihugu kiracahaye indaro impunzi z’abarundi bagiye barahungirayo mu bihe bitandukanye Uburundi bwagiye buraja mu ndyane za poritike n’amoko
 Ubu muri Tanzania haharugwa abarundi b’impunzi barenga 127
000 hakurikijwe ibiharuro vya HCR
 Ushizeko abari mu bihugu bibanyi vya Repubrika y’intwaro rusangi ya Congo, Urwanda na Uganda, abarundi b’impunzi barenga 258
000
 Ahandi hari abarundi b’impunzi nk’uko vyerekanwa na HCR:  Muri Tanzania hariho kandi abarundi barenga 42
000 b'impunzi ariko  batagihabwa imfasho na HCR
 Abo bahoze ari impuzi z’abarundi ubu babaye abenegihugu ba Tanzania bavuga ko HCR yari yarabemereye imfashanyo yo gutangura ubuzima bushasha ariko ko gushika ubu atayo bararonswa
 Icegera c’uwuserukira HCR muri Tanzania, George Kuchio, avuga ati: “Hagize ubundi buryo buboneka, buvuye mu basanzwe bafasha, nta nkeka buzoza gufasha abo bantu kuduza urugero rwo kubaho neza
”
Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya aracarondera kwigarurira igice kinini ca Ukraine, nk’uko bivugwa n’ibisata vya Amerika bijejwe igendereza
 Hagati aho, abategetsi ba Amerika babona ko ingabo za Moscou ziruhishijwe cane n’iyi ntambara, bakabona ko ico bashoboye ubu ari ukwigarurira uduce duto tw’ubutaka bwa Ukraine
 Bisigura ko iyi ntambara ishobora kumara igihe kirekire, nk’uko umukuru w’ikigo c’igihugu kijejwe igendereza, Avril Haines, abivuga
 Mu kwa gatatu, Moscou yafashe ingingo yo gushira inguvu zose ku karere ka Donbas kari mu buseruko bwa Ukraine inyuma y’aho inaniriwe no gufata umugwa mukuru Kyiv n’ibindi bisagara
 Putin aracafise intumbero zisa n’izo yari afise igihe intambara itangura, ukwigarurira Ukraine yose, nk’uko uyu mutegetsi mukuru w’igendereza rya Amerika Haines abivuga
 Ariko, avuga ko Uburusiya bushobora kudashika kuri iyi ntumbero ubu bwa vuba
  Yabwiye inama y’ishami ry’ubucuruzi muri Amerika ati: "Hano turabona ko hari ubudasa hagati y’intumbero za gisirikare Putin ashaka mu kiringo gito, n’ubushobozi bw’igisirikare ciwe, bikaba bidahuye n’ivyo yifuza ndetse n’ivyo ingabo zishobora gushikako"
 Kuva aho bunaniriwe gushika ku ntumbero yabwo yo gufata Kyiv, Uburusiya bwibanze kwigarurira ubutaka mu karere ka Donbas  - akarere kagutse karimwo amahinguriro, Putin akitwaza ko Ukraine ikorera ihonyabwoko abavuga ikirusiya
 Ingabo z’Uburusiya zarateye intambwe muri ako karere, aho ziherutse kwigarurira igisagara ca Severodonetsk, ariko zikaba zigenda bukebuke na rirya ingabo za Ukraine zibandanya zihagararako
 Mw’ijambo rya mbere ashikirije icese kuva mu kwa gatanu ku vyerekeye ingene igendereza rya Amerika ribona iyi ntambara, umupfasoni Haines avuga ko igitero c’Uburusiya gishobora kubandanya “igihe kirekire” kandi ko “ishusho ibandanya iba mbi”
 Avuga ko ibisata bijejwe igendereza bibona ibintu bitatu bishoboka ku kungene iyi ntambara ishobora kubandanya, ikintu gishoboka cane kikaba ari uko intambara ishobora kubandanya ku muvuduko muto, aho Uburusiya “buzogenda bufata uturere ariko ntihagire ico bifasha”
 Ibindi bishoboka, ariko ku rugero ruto, harimwo ko Uburusiya bushobora gutera intambwe ikomeye, canke bugashobora gutsimbataza ibirindiro vyabwo ku rubuga rw'intambara,  Ukraine nayo igashobora gutera intambwe ntoya
 Ibi bishobora gusigura ko Moscou ishobora gukoresha cane uburyo bw’intambara butamenyerewe mu gutera abansi bayo, harimwo n’ibitero nyabwonko, kugenzura amasoko ntanganguvu n’ibirwanisho ruhonyanganda vy’ubumara
 Haines yashikirije aya majambo ejo ku wa gatatu inyuma y’aho abategetsi ba OTAN biyemeje gushigikira Ukraine mu gihe cose bizoba ari ngombwa – mu kwongereza ingabo zayo ku mugabane wose w’Ubulaya no mu kwemerera Finland na  Suède/Sweden kwinjira muri iri huriro ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe
 Umunyamabanga mukuru wa OTAN Jens Stoltenberg avuga ko izi ari zo mpinduka zikomeye gusumba izimaze gukorwa inyuma ya ya ntambara y’ukwikekana (Guerre Froide/Cold War), aho Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika avuga ko OTAN   “izokomezwa mu buryo bwose ku mpande zose  - ku butaka, mu kirere no mu mazi”
 Yishura ku kibazo c’uko ibi bihugu bibiri vyo mu Buraruko bishobora kwinjira mw’ishirahamwe OTAN, Perezida Putin yagirije iri huriro rya gisirikare ko ririko ryunyura icuka kibi n’ibigirankana
 Igihe yari mu rugendo muri Turkmenistan, Putin yavuze ati: "Mu gihe ingabo n’ibikoresho vyoramuka birungitswe,  bizoba ngombwa ko [Uburusiya] bwihora”
 Hagati aho, reta y’Ubwongereza yiteguye guha Ukraine imfashanyo ya gisirikare ingana n’imiriyaridi 1
2 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika, hafi incuro zibiri z’iyo Ubwongereza bumaze guha gushika ubu iki gihugu gihanganye n’Uburusiya
 Amerika yonyene niyo imaze guha Ukraine imfashanyo isumba iy’Ubwongereza
 Umukuru w’igihugu ca Ukraine Volodymyr Zelensky avuga ko igihugu ciwe gikeneye imiriyaridi zababa zitanu z’amadorari y’abanyamerika buri kwezi kugira ngo gishobore guhangana n’Uburusiya

Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zigiye kwongereza ingabo ku mugabane wa Bulaya inyuma y’aho ibihugu bigize OTAN/NATO vyumvikaniye ku “mpinduka zikomeye” kubera igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine
 Icicaro kizokwamaho kigiye gushingwa muri Pologne, mu gihe amato y’intambara ya Amerika azorungikwa muri Espagne, indege nazo zirungikwe mu Bwongereza, nayo abasirikare barwanira ku butaka barungikwe muri Roumanie/Romania
 Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika avuga ko OTAN ari “nkenerwa gusumba uko yahoze”
 Iri huriro ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe ririko riranagurwa gusumba uko ryavyigeze kuva kuri ya ntambara y’ukwikekana (Guerre froide/Cold War), nk’uko bivugwa n’umunyamabanga mukuru wa OTAN Jens Stoltenberg
 Iyi nteguro nshasha yo kwishura ku gitero c’Uburusiya isigura ko ingabo zirenga 300
000 zizoba zimeze magabo mu mwaka uza, zivuye kuri 40
000 zari zisanzwe zihari ubu
 Perezida Biden yabwiye abari mu nama yabo yabera ku mugwa mukuru wa Espagne, Madrid, ko OTAN  “izokomezwa mu buryo bwose ku mpande zose  - ku butaka, mu kirere no mu mazi”
 Ubushikiranganji bw’Ubwongereza bujejwe kwivuna abansi na bwo nyene buvuga ko buriko burongereza ingabo zishobora gukoreshwa na OTAN mu kwivunira umwansi hamwe, mu gutegura amato y’intambara, indege z’intambara n’ingabo zirwanira ku butaka – n’aho ubu bushikiranganji buvuga ko budashobora gutanga amakuru arambuye ku bitigiri kuko ari “ibanga rya gisirikare”
 Iri tangazo rya Amerika risigura ko igiye kwongereza inguvu za gisirikare ku mugabane wose cane cane mu buseruko bwa Bulaya, ahagiye gushingwa icicaro gishasha ca gisirikare c’iri huriro ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe
 Perezida Biden ashimangira ko iri huriro ryiyemeje “gukingira agace ako ari ko kose” k’ubutaka bwaryo, akavuga ati: "Tuba twavyiyumviriye iyo tuvuze ko igitero ku gihugu kimwe ari igitero ku bihugu vyose”
 Muri izi ngingo harimwo: ·  Kwongereza amato y’intambara ya Amerika muri Espagne kuva kuri ane gushika kuri atandatu ·  Kwongereza "ingabo zikurakuranywa muri Roumanie zigizwe n’abarwanyi 3000 hamwe n’uwundi murwi w’abasirikare 2000 ·  Iyindi mirwi ibiri y’abasirikare barwanira mu kirere bakoresha indege zo mu bwoko bwa F-35 mu Bwongereza ·  Kwongereza uburyo bwo kurwanira mu kirere mu Budagi no mu Butaliyano
 Ubwongereza bwarongereje hafi incuro zibiri abasirikare bufise muri Estonia, ku ngabo zirenga 1600 muri ico gihugu
 Abenshi bazorungikiwa mu bihugu vy’akarere ka Balte, n’aho ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi buvuga ko izi ngabo zongerejwe zishobora kwama zigavye mu gihe zizoba zisubiye mu gihugu
 Muri iri koraniro, abategetsi ba OTAN bumvikanye kwemerera ibihugu vyahoze ataho vyegamiye vyo mu buraruko Finland na Suède/Sweden kwinjira muri iri huriro, ariko igisabo cabo kikazotegerezwa kwemezwa n’ibi bihugu vyose 30 bigize OTAN
 Perezida Biden avuga ko ibi ari “neza na neza” ivyo Perezida Vladimir Putin w’Uburusiya atashaka, kandi ko ingingo yiwe yo gutera Ukraine yamugizeko ingaruka mbi
 Umunyamabanga mukuru wa OTAN Stoltenberg avuga ko Finland na Suède bimaze gutumirwa kwinjira muri iri huriro rya gisirikare, akavuga ko “ari vyo bihugu bizoba vyinjiye ningoga kuva ribaho”, kandi ko yizeye ko bigeye kwihutishwa
 Ibi bihugu bibiri bisaba kwinjira muri iri shirahamwe bitegerezwa kwerekana ko bigendera ku ngingo ngenderwako za OTAN  muri poritike, mu mategeko no mu gisirikare – ikintu kigiye kuba vuba bwango muri ibi bihugu vyo mu buraruko bwa Bulaya
 Stoltenberg avuga ko Ukraine ishobora kubandanya yizeye imfashanyo y’iri huriro mu guhangana n’igitero c’Uburusiya “igihe cose bizoba nkenerwa”, yongerako y’uko Ukraine iriko irwanira ubwigenge bwayo ariko kandi n’indangagaciro isangiye na OTAN
 Avuga ko ibihugu biri muri iri shirahamwe vyumvikanye guha Ukraine “imfashanyo iboneka”, irimwo igitoro, imiti, imyambaro yo kwikingira amasasu, ibikoresho vyo kurwanya za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) hamwe n’ibikoresho vyo kurwanya ama mines
 Iri koraniro rirerekana integuro ngenderwako nshasha y’iri huriror rivuga ko Uburusiya ari bwo “bubangamiye cane umutekano w’ibi bihugu vyishize hamwe be n’amahoro n’umutekano w’akarere ka Bulaya na Atlantiki [Euro-Atlantic]”
 Rivuga kandi ko “tutohava twibaza ko Uburusiya budashoboye guhungabanya ubwigenge n’ubusugire bw’ibi bihugu vyishize hamwe”
 Perezida Putin  ntahakana ko hashobora kwaduka icuka kibi hagati y’Uburusiya na Suède hamwe na Finland inyuma yo kwinjira muri OTAN, akavuga kandi ko Moscou ishobora kwihora uko vyokenerwa mu gihe OTAN  yoshinga ibirindiro muri ibi bihugu
 Avuga ko abategetsi ba OTAN  bashaka “kwishira hejuru gusumba ibindi bihugu vyose no kwiyagurira uturere”, ariko akavuga kandi ko Uburusiya ata “ngorane” bufise kuri Finland na Suède kwinjira muri iryo huriro

Bernard Bankukira BBC Gahuzamiryango Kimwe mu bintu bituma Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo yama mu ntambara igihe kinini ni “ubutegetsi bwayo bugoyagoya", ibi bivugwa n’umwigisha wa kaminuza, Filip Reyntjens, umuhinga ku karere k’ibiyaga binini vya Afrika
 Mu kiganiro na BBC Gahuzamiryango, uyu mushakashatsi w’umubirigi avuga ko ubutegetsi bwa DR Congo kuva kera wasanga "budashobora kurangura amabanga yabwo nkenerwa, harimwo kugenzura ubutaka bwayo no kubungabunga ubusugire bwayo”, akavuga ko ari ingorane y’ubutegetsi isanzwe ihari kuva ku butegetsi bwa Mobutu
 Avuga ati: “Mobutu kuva mu myaka ya 1970, yagiye arasambura bukebuke iki gihugu kitagishoboye kurangura amabanga shingiro yaco kuva kera cane”
 Abona ko uku kugoyagoya kw’ubutegetsi bwa Congo kwibonekeza kandi no mu gisirikare cayo
 Kuva inyuma y’intambara yo mu mwaka wa 1996-1997 yomoye Mobutu Sese Seko ku butegetsi yari amazeko imyaka irenga 30, Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo (RDC/DRC), yahoze yitwa Zaïre, ni nk’uko ata mahoro arama irigera ironka
 Kuva ico gihe, iki gihugu co mu karere k’ibiyaga binini kigira kabiri mu bunini ku mugabane wa Afrika, camye kirangwamwo intambara, cane cane mu ntara zo mu buseruko, ahavugwa ubu imirwi irenga 100 yitwaje ibirwanisho yama iriko irahungabanya umutekano w’abanyagihugu
 Filip Reyntjens avuga ko igisirikare ca Congo  - igisirikare ca Zaïre ku butegetsi bwa Mobutu –  ari co “cirori c’ubu butegetsi bugoyagoya”
 Ati: “Uribuka n’igihe Congo yikurako M23 mu 2013, vyakozwe n’ingabo mpuzamakungu zaje gushigikira MONUSCO zibona kwomora M23, si igisirikare ca Congo cabirukanye”
 “Eka no mu ntambara ya kabiri ya Congo mu 1998 si igisirikare ca Congo ca Laurent-Désiré Kabila carwanye, harwanye incuti zayo cane cane za Angola na Zimbabwe  zaje gutabara ubutegetsi bwa Kabila
 “Ni bo bahagaritse iyi mihari ibiri y’inyeshamba, ico gihe yari MLC ya Jean-Pierre Bemba yafashwa na Uganda, hamwe na RCD yari ifashwe mu mugongo n’Urwanda”
 Ku bwiwe, ingabo za Congo ntizarwanye, ariko ubu hariho akarusho “kuko ubu ingabo za FARDC zirarwana, n’aho bidashemeye”
 Ati: “Bararwana, ariko biraboneka ko n’aho boba bahanganye n’umwansi asanzwe, ntaco bashikako, ni ko vyagenze nk’akarorero kuri M23, haba i Bunaganara  canke no mu tundi turere twa teritware ya Rutshuru”
 Ariko n’aho avuga ko igisirikare c’iki gihugu kigoyagoya, abona ko ubu hariho iterambere, ko ubu gifise inguvu, ugereranije n’igihe intambara ya mbere ya Congo intangura mu 1996
 Ati: “Ico gihe, igisirikare ca Zaïre nta n’ubwo carwanye
 Nta ntambara yabaye, barahunze imbere y’inyeshamba za AFDL ico gihe zafashwa na Uganda hamwe n’Urwanda”
 Hampande y’ubu butegetsi bugoyagoya, Reyntjens abona kandi ko harimwo n’inyungu z’akarere zituma ibihugu bibanyi vyiyagurira uturere tw’intambara
 Ati: “Aha turabona nka Uganda, u Rwanda, hamwe n’Uburundi ariko ku rugero kanaka, ariko kandi tutibagiye na  Angola, mu 1996-97 , vyakoreye intambara yo hagati yavyo bizikorera ku butaka bw’iki gihugu kigoyagoya, citwa Zaïre ico gihe, ubu kikaba citwa Congo”
 Muri kino gihe, igisirikare ca DRC gihanganye n’umuhari M23 uherutse kwigarurira igisagara ca Bunagana kiri ku rubibie iki gihugu gihana na Uganda
 Kuva kera reta ya Congo yamye yagiriza u Rwanda ko rufasha umuhari wa M23, ivyo leta y’u Rwanda nayo yamye yamirira kure
 Abajijwe kuri iki kibazo, Reyntjens na we nyene avuga ko ubu ata vyemezo bifadika bafise vyerekana imfashanyo u Rwanda rwoba ruha M23, ariko akemeza ko “abari mu mugambwe FPR mu Rwanda bafasha cane M23 mu bijanye na poritike hamwe na diplomasi”
 Ati: “Gusa sinzi neza, ariko n’aho ubuserukizi bwa Amerika i Kinshasa bwagirije amenya u Rwanda ko rufasha M23 mu buryo bwa gisirikare, ubu sindabona neza nk’uko vyari mu 2012-2013, ivyemezo bifadika vy’imfashanyo ya gisirikare u Rwanda rwoba ruha M23”
 Hagati aho, afatiye ku vyabaye aho hambere abona ko bitoba bitangaje ko u Rwanda rwovugwa muri kino gihe mu buseruko bwa Congo
 Ati: “U Rwanda ruzwi ko rwakoreye muri ako karere ibikorwa vya gisirikare, ruragenzura umwanya utari muto ako karere k’ubuseruko bwa Congo
 Uretse izi ntara zibiri z’ubuseruko bwa Congo, Kivu ya Ruguru na Kivu y’Epfo, rwarageze kure mbere, rushika za Kasai na za Katanga muri ya ntambara ya kabiri yo kuva mu 1998 gushika 2003
 “Rero ku Rwanda sinovuga ko ako gace ari ubutaka bwarwo, ariko ni akarere rwakoreramwo ibikorwa vya gisirikare, vya poritike, ariko cane cane vya poritike"
 Uretse abavugizi ba reta y’u Rwanda bahakana ibi birego, igihe cose Perezida Paul Kagame abajijwe iki kibazo, yama asigura ko igihugu ciwe ata ruhara gifise mu bibera muri Congo
 Hagati aho, inyuma y’intambara ya mbere yo kwomora ubutegetsi bwa Mobutu yari irongowe na Laurent-Désiré Kabila, ivy’uko u Rwanda rwafashije umuhari AFDL vyagiye gushimangirwa n’uko Jenerali James Kabarebe abaye umukuru w’igisirikare gishasha ca Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi yari irongowe na Laurent-Désiré Kabila
 Ku bwa Reyntjens, ni ibisanzwe ko Perezida Kagame ahakana uruhara rw’u Rwanda kuko rwamye ruhakana kuva kera
 Ati: “Yarahakanye mu 1996, arahakana mu 1998, mu 2012/2013 igihe no mu ncuti ziwe ata n’umwe yemeye ivyo yavuze”
 Ibiganiro bihagarariwe na Kenya vyatanguye mu misi iheze, vyatanze umwizero ko kumbure amahoro ashobora kugaruka muri aka karere, ariko ibintu ahubwo vyateye vyunyuka inyuma y’aho umuhari M23 wirukaniwe muri vyo, wagirizwa gutera ingabo za reta, mugabo wowo ukavuga ko wasotowe
 Inyuma y’aho, reta ya Kinshasa yatangaje ko umuhari wa M23 ari uw’iterabwoba
 Intambara hagati ya reta ya DR Congo n’umuhari M23 yatumye imigenderanire hagati y’iki gihugu n’u Rwanda isubira gutosekara inyuma y’imyaka ibiri yari myiza, kuva Perezida Felix Tshisekedi ashitse ku butegetsi
 Ivya M23 vyasubiye kuvugwa cane mu mpera z’umwaka uheze, inyuma y’imyaka yababa cumi yari irangiye ni ukuvuga kuva mu 2013 igihe itsindiwe n’ingabo mvamakungu, ata gakacira
 Ikintu gitangaza Reyntjens ni uko icuka kibi hagati ya DR Congo n’u Rwanda casubiye kuvyuka ico gihugu cinjiye mw’ishirahamwe rya Afrika y’Ubuseruko (EAC)
 Ati: “Budakeye na kabiri  yinjiye, niho DRC yaca itangura kwagiriza Urwanda ko ruvogera ubutaka bwayo”
 Abona ko ari ikintu gitangaje na rirya amaso y’isi yose yari ahanze u Rwanda rwariko rwitegurira kwakira inama ya Commonwealth iherutse kurangira ku mugwa mukuru, Kigali
 Yongera ati: “Ibitero vya M23 n’imfashanyo ivugwa y’u Rwanda vyaje hasigaye indwi nk’imwe canke zibiri ngo inama ya Commonwealth itangure i Kigali”
 Ku wa 20 Ruheshi uno mwaka, abakuru b’ibihugu bigize ishirahamwe rya Afrika y’Ubuseruko (EAC)  mu nama yabo i Nairobi, umugwa mukuru wa Kenya, kugira bige kibazo c’amahoro n’umutekano  muri Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo (DRC),  bafashe ingingo y’uko harungikwa vuba ingabo z’iri shirahamwe kugira zituze imirwi y’inyeshamba ivugwa muri aka karere
 Reyntjens wewe nta cizere afise ko izi ngabo zizohava zirungikwa, kubera ico abona ko ari inzitizi zishingiye ku kungene ibintu bimeze muri kino gihe
 Ati: “Nibaza ko imbere yo gushinga izi ngabo ari ukubanza kwitonda, bakabanza gukuraho inzitizi zimwe zimwe
 Biragoye kwiyumvira ko muri kino gihe, uravye ingene ibintu bimeze hagati ya Congo n’u Rwanda ukungene ingabo z’u Rwanda zoba ziri muri iki gisirikare c’akarere kigiye kugarukana amahoro muri Congo
 Ni ibintu bidashoboka”
 “Eka mbere n’aho twofatira ku migenderanire idatomoye hagati ya Congo na Uganda, jewe vyontangaza n’aho hari ingabo za Uganda ziri muri Congo ariko mu rwego rutandukanye n’uru, rwo kurwanya ADF”
 Ku bwiwe, igisirikare nk’iki gishobora gukora mu gihe coba kigizwe gusa n’ingabo ziva mu bihugu bidafise uruhara mu ndyane, cane cane Tanzania na Kenya
 Ati: “Tanzania iboneka cane ko ataho yegamiye ku buyo ishobora kuba muri izi ngabo, co kimwe na Kenya nayo nyene ifatwa ko ataho yegamiye muri iyi ntambara
 Sudani y’Epfo nayo nyene ntaho yegamiye, ariko ifise ibibazo vyinshi biyihanze ku buryo idashobora kubamwo”
 “Ibihugu vyorungika ingabo vyoba bidafise aho vyegamiye, ibi ndabivuze kubera ko izi ngabo z’akarere zizoshobora kurangura igikorwa uko gitegerezwa mu gihe zitokwikekwa ko ata kintu cinyegeje ibihugu vyazo birondera
 “Aha rero biragoye kwiyumvira ingene ingabo za Uganda, iz’u Rwanda n’iz’Uburundi zoba ziri ku butaka bwa Congo ku buryo atawokwikeka ko zifise icinyegeje, ibi navyo siko vyogenda ku ngabo za Kenya n’iza Tanzania”
 Reyntjens yibutsa ko ingabo za Tanzania, isanzwe iri muri ca gisirikare mpuzamakungu, ziri kumwe n’iza Afrika y’Epfo hamwe n’iza Malawi, ari zo zashoboye gutsinda M23 mu 2013

Inyuma y’aho ibihugu bibiri vya Afrika vyahoze bitwarwa gikoloni n’Ubufaransa vyinjiriye muri  Commonwealth, Paul Melly yihweza ibintu n’ibindi arasigura igitera amero ibihugu birondera kwinjira muri uyu muryango ukoresha ururimi rw’icongereza
 Gabon na Togo vyafashe ingingo yo gukomeza imigenderanire yavyo mu ntumbero yo kuraba ko vyogabanya ukwishigikiza Ubufaransa
 Vyakiriwe mu muryango watangujwe n’ibihugu vyahoze bitwarwa gikoloni n’Ubwongereza ariko bivamwo birugururira imiryango ibindi
 Ibi bihugu bibiri vya Afrika bito bikoresha igifaransa ubu bibaye ibigira 55 na 56 vyinjiye muri iri shirahamwe
 U Rwanda rwinjiye mu 2009 mu gihe Mozambique yari yinjiye mu 1995
 Ibi bihugu bibiri nta migenderanire idasanzwe vyigeze bigiranira n’Ubwongereza muri kahise
 Kubona vyafashe ingingo yo kwinjira mw’ishirahamwe Commonwealth vyerekana ko ari umuryango ngirakamaro mu bijanye n’imigenderanire n’akaranga, n'"ubutegetsi bwiyoroheje" (soft power) ku rubuga mpuzamakungu
 Vyerekana kandi uruhara rw’icongereza nk’ururimi rw’ubudandaji, ubuhinga na poritike mpuzamakungu, n’akamaro ko kwubaka ubucuti n’ibihugu bitandukanye mu ntumbero yo gutsimbataza iterambere no kugira ngo ijwi ryavyo ryumvikane mu bijanye n’imigenderanire
 Kuri Gabon na Togo, u Rwanda ruratera intege: inyuma y’imyaka 13 gusa rwinjiye, rwashoboye kwakira ikoraniro ry’iri shirahamwe, ryitabiriwe n’abakuru b’ibihugu n’amareta bavuye mu mpande zose z’isi, n’aho hari abatashoboye kuhashika, harimwo Perezida Cyril Ramaphosa  wa Africa y’Epfo
  Ukwinjira kwa  Gabon na Togo muri Commonwealth kuje kandi mu gihe imigenderanire hagati ya Afrika n’Ubufaransa igenda itosekara
 Igitigiri kitari gito c’abanyagihugu bakiri bato baba mu bisagara basaba abategetsi b’ibihugu vyabo guhagarika ikoreshwa ry’ifaranga rya CFA ryihetse kw’ifaranga rya Bulaya, euro, nk’uko biri mu masezerano ahagarariwe na reta i Paris
 Ikibazo c’ingabo z’Ubufaransa kandi muri Sahel ntikibonwa kumwe
 Rero biboneka ko abenshi mu rwaruka rwa Togo na Gabon bashobora kwakiriza yompi ingingo yo kwinjira muri iri shirahamwe rinini kw’isi rikoresha icongereza
 Ibi bifasha kunagura isura y’ubutegetsi bw’ibi bihugu bibiri vyaboneka ko mu kiringo c’imyaka itari mike, bwaboneka nk’ikimenyetso kidasanzwe c’imigenderanire kama ya hafi cane hagati y’abategetsi ba Afrika n’Ubufaransa – mu ciswe "la  françafrique"
 Harigeze kuba igihe aho ingingo nk’iyi yashobora gutera umwikomo mu bategetsi ba Paris batinya ko ikibanza bafise mu karere ko musi y’ubugaragwa bwa Sahara gishobora gutakara
 Ariko ubu ubutegetsi bw’Ubufaransa bugenda bworosha
 Imvo nkizi nyene zo kwagura ubucuti no kugira imigenderanire n’ibihugu bishasha zatumye iri shirahamwe rigenzi rya Commonwealth rikoresha igifaransa ryaguka, hakavuka icitwa Organisation Internationale de la Francophonie (OIF), twosigura mu kirundi tuti “Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ry’ibihugu bikoresha igifaransa”
 Ubu rigizwe n’ibihugu n’amareta 88 – harimwo u Rwanda,  aho mbere n’uwahoze ari umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire warwo, Louise Mushikiwabo, ari we Munyamabanga mukuru waryo muri kino gihe
 Ibiro vyaryo mu karere ka Afrika y’Uburengero n’iyo hagati bikaba biri muri Togo na Gabon, kandi naryo nyene ririko riraguka
 Mu kwa gatatu umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire wa Ghana Shirley Ayorkor Botchwey yatangaje ko igihugu ciwe, naco cahoze gitwarwa gikoloni n’Ubwongereza kikaba kandi cari umunywanyi w’iri shirahamwe OIF nk’indorerezi kuva mu 2006, cari kigiye kuba umunywanyi yuzuye w’iri shirahamwe
 Ghana, nk’igihugu gifise inzego za demokarasi zikomeye n’ubutunzi bukomeye, kizoba ari kimwe mu gitigiri kigenda ciyongera c’ibihugu biri muri ano mashirahamwe yompi ya Commonwealth na Francophonie – ku mvo zo gukomeza imigenderanire
 Ibihugu bibanyi vyayo hafi vyose muri Afrika y’Uburengero bikoresha igifaransa mbere reta igenda ifata ingendo yo kwigisha urwaruka rwayo kugira ngo bungukire muri iyi nyubako y’ubutunzi, imico na poritike – nk’akarorero ubu hari amashure 50 yigisha muri izi ndimi zompi
 Hanyuma kandi nta kwibagira n’irindi shirahamwe rito rigenda rikomera kandi rigifise ikibanza, ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu bikoresha ururimi rw’igi Portugal, rizwi nka Community of Portuguese Language Countries (CPLP) - ibihugu biri muri iri shirahamwe hafi vyose ni ivya Afrika
 Ariko aya mashirahamwe yose atatu - CPLP, Francophonie na Commonwealth – ahanganye n’ikibazo ngorabahizi c’ugukomeza intwaro ibereye, intwaro rusangi n’agateka ka zina muntu – ikibazo gihanze Ubumwe bwa Afrika n’amashirahamwe amwe amwe ahuza uturere twa Afrika, cane cane nka Communauté économique des États de l'Afrique de l'Ouest/Economic Community of West African States (CEDEAO/ECOWAS)
 Amashirahamwe yompi, Commonwealth na OIF, ararungika abahinga gufasha ibihugu gutsimbataza integuro zavyo z’amatora, ariko iyo hageze ku bijanye n’ibisabwa kugira ngo igihugu kanaka cakirwe, basa n’abugururira bose imiryango, bakitaho gusa guhimiriza buke buke hagufata umurongo ugumye
 Togo yarongowe n’umukuru w’igihugu yamenyekanye cane ko yatwaza umukazo, Gnassingbé Eyadéma, kuva mu 1967 gushika 2005, kandi kuva ico gihe gushika ubu irongowe n’umuhungu wiwe, Faure Gnassingbé
 Umukuru w’igihugu ca Gabon, Ali Ben Bongo Ondimba, ni umuhungu wa Omar Bongo, yarongoye ico gihugu kuva 1967 gushika 2009, akaba yarinjiye no mu gihuhusi c’imigambwe myinshi mu myaka ya 1990, ariko yagiye yinengesera kugira ngo umugambwe wiwe ubandanye ari wo uri hejuru, kandi umuryango wiwe na wo nyene ubandanye ufise uruhara muri reta
 Imbere y’uko asubirira se wiwe mu kibanza c’umukuru w’igihugu, Ali Bongo yari umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi
 Itangazo ryasohowe na Commonwealth ritangaza iyinjira rya Togo na Gabon ryavuga riti: "Muri vyinshi bisabwa kugira ngo igihugu cinjire muri Commonwealth, harimwo ikivuga ko igihugu gisaba kwinjira gitegerezwa kwerekana ko ciyemeje gutsimbataza intwaro rusangi kandi kikagendera mu nzira za demokarasi, harimwo amatora meza kandi yisanzuye be n’inzego nshingamateka”
 Ariko Perezida Paul Kagame w’u Rwanda, n’aho ata nkeka ko mu makungu akengurukwa  kubera iterambere yazanye mu gihugu ciwe mu bijanye n’ubutunzi n’imibano, amashirahamwe aharanira agateka ka zina muntu amwagiriza ko atwaza agahotoro
 Abamunegura bavuga ko abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi bwiwe batotezwa kandi bagashirwa ku ruhande
 Perezida Kagame avuga ko ubutegetsi bwiwe bwubahiriza uburenganzira bwa kiremwa muntu, kandi ko ata “muntu n’umwe mu Rwanda ari mw’ibohero atategerezwa kuba ari yo ari”
 Kuri Gabon, amatora y’umukuru w’igihugu ategekanijwe mu mwaka uza azoba ari igipimo c’intwaro ibereye
 Ariko kuri Togo hoho, igipimo gisa n’ikitatevye
 Ku musi nyene Commonwealth itangaza ibi, abategetsi baciye babuza imyiyerekano yari itegekanijwe n’umuhari utavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi, Dynamique Monseigneur Kpodzro (DMK), mu ntumbero yo kwiyamiriza ubuzima buzimvye, hamwe n’ico wita intwaro mbi n’akarenganyo
 DMK yaciye yungururiza iyi myiyerekano ku wa 16 z’ukw’indwi
 Kazoba ari akaryo keza ko kuraba nimba muri Togo reta izoba yiteguye kwiyorosha, nk’umunywanyi mushasha wa Commonwealth
 Paul Melly ni umuhanuzi mu gisata ca Afrika mu kigo Chatham House i Londres

Umwana w’umuhungu yari yatakaye yatowe ari muzima inyuma y’indwi yamaze ari mu kiringoti gitwara imicafu y’abantu, aha ni mu Budagi
 Uyu mwana w’imyaka umunani yamenyekanye kw’izina rimwe gusa rya Joe, yabuze mu muryango wiwe uri mu karere ka Oldenburg ku wa 17 z’uku kwa gatandatu, ivyatumye igipolisi gitangura igikorwa co kumurondera
 Yahavuye atorwa ku wa gatandatu, igihe umuntu yariko yirenganira yumva ijwi ry’umuntu mu kinogo c’imicafu (regard) gipfundikiye
 Igipolisi kivuga ko ata muntu cagiriza icaha, kikavuga ko uyo mwana w’umuhungu yinjiye muri ico kiringoti gitwara imicafu ku musi yaburirwa irengero
 Inyuma y’aho abajejwe kuzimya imiriro y’ivyaduka bavaniye uyu mwana muri ico kiringoti – capima imetero hafi 300 uvuye muhira iwabo – yaciye asimbanwa kwa muganga kugira ngo bamupime nimba atoba yaranduye indwara ziturutse ku bukonje, ariko nta bikomere bikomeye yari afise
 Igipolisi nico cahavuye gitangaza iyi nkuru giciye ku rubuga rwa Twitter: "Joe w’imyaka umunani aracari muzima!" "Ku nkuru twahawe n’abanyagihugu, twarashoboye gutora Joe ari mu kinogo c’imicafu," nk’uko umukuru w’igipolisi Johann Kühme abivuga
 "Ikintu nyamukuru ni uko akiri muzima kandi yaciye asimbanwa ku bitaro aho ariko arakurikiranwa neza
 Ubu twese twohumura”
 Se wiwe yabwiye ibinyamakuru vyo muri ako karere ko Joe “yari ameze neza” uravye ivyo yaciyemwo
 Hari abibaza ingene uyu mwana w’umuhungu yinjiye muri ico kinogo, ariko ejo ku wa kabiri igipolisi cavuze ko yikweze akinjiramwo hanyuma akaza “kubura ivyo yishimikiza”

Abantu batari munsi ya 46 batowe bapfuye bari mw’ikamyo yahebwe ku nkengera za San Antonio, muri Texas
 Umwe mu bakora mu gisata co kuzimya imiriro yavuze ko abantu 16, barimwo abana bane, bajanywe mu bitaro
 Abarokotse bari “bashushe ubakozeko” kandi bababaye kubera kuba bahuye n’ubushuhe bwinshi
 San Antonio, iri ku birometero 250 uvuye ku rubibe rwa Mexique na Amerika, ni inzira ikomeye ikoreshwa n’abantu bajabukana abantu mu kinyegero
 Abacuruza abantu  akenshi barakoresha amakamyo mu gutwara abimukira badafise ivyangombwa bahejeje kubonanira mu turere twa kure  iyo bamaze kwinjira muri Amerika
 Umukuru w’igisagara ca San Antonio Ron Nirenberg yavuze ati: “bari bafise imiryango… Ni akaga
”  Abajejwe gushika aho vyihutirwa ubwa mbere bahashitse isaha 12 z’umugoroba mu masaha y’aho  inyuma yo kwumva amakuru y’uko hari ikiziga cabonetse, nk’uko umukuru w’igisata co kuzimya imiriro muri San Antonio Charles Hood yabibwiye abamenyeshamakuru
 Ati: “Ntawari yiteze ko twugurura ikamyo tugasangayo ibirundo vy’abantu bapfuye
 Nta n’umwe yari yavuye mu biro yibaza ivyo”
 Yanavuze kandi ko iyo kamyo, yari yatawe n’umudereva wayo, ata cuma gitanga akayaga yari ifise gikora kandi ko ata mazi yo kunywa yari ari muri yo
 Muri iki gihe c’ici i San  Antonio harashushe cane, ubushuhe bukaba bwari mu bipimo vya Celcius 39
4 ku wa mbere, kandi bikekwa ko abo bantu bashobora kuba bishwe n’ugushuhirwa cane hamwe n’umwumira
 Ministre wa Mexique ajejwe imigenderanire, Marcelo Ebrard,  yavuze ko abanya-Guatemala babiri bari mu bajanywe mu bitaro
 Ariko ko amamuko y’abandi bahuye n’ako kaga ntiyashotse amenyekana
 Hari abantu batatu bafashwe n’igiporisi hanyuma amatohoza akaba yashizwe ku rwego rw’igihugu
 Edward Reyna, umukozi ajejwe gucungera  ahagurishirizwa imbaho n’ibindi bikoresho vyo kwubaka hafi y’aho yavuze ko atatangajwe no gushika atonze ku kazi kiwe ko mw’ijoro hanyuma akakirwa n’iyo nkuru
 Avuga ko atacirirwa araharura kangahe amaze kubona abantu basimba bava mw’itereni ica hafi y’aho iyo kamyo yatowe
 Umukuru w’intara ya Texas w’umu republicain Greg Abbott yegetse kuri prezida Joe Biden urupfu rw’abo bantu  avuga ko ari “ingaruka za poritike yiwe yo kwugurura imbibe”
 Ikibazo c’abimukira ni ikibazo giteye impari za porike  nyinshi cane muri Amerika, aho mu kwezi kwa gatanu igitigiri ca mbere kinini c’abantu 239
000 batagira ivya ngombwa bapfunzwe binjiye mu gihugu bava muri Mexique- benshi bakaba bafata ingendo zibangamye cane
 Ubu abategetsi bajejwe kwubahiriza amategeko muri Amerika bari hafi yo kurenza igitigiri ca mbere kinini ca miriyoni 1,73 c’abantu bafashwe bajabutse urubibe mu 2021, mu gihe hakomeje kuba ibitigiri binini vy’abantu bajabuka bavuye mu bihugu vyo muri Amerika yo hagati nka Honduras, Guatemala na El Salvador
 Mu gihe bahunga ubukene n’intureka muri Amerika yo hagati, benshi muri abo bantu baruhira guha amafaranga menshi cane abo bacuruzi  bajabukana abantu mu kinyegero kugira babajabutse urubibe rwa Amerika
 Muri iyi myaka, harabaye ubundi burorero nk’ubwo bw’aho abimukira bagwa mu ngendo, ariko ntivyari bwashike aho abangana gutyo bapfira rimwe nk’uko
 Ako kaga kamaze kumenyekana, musenyeri wa katorika wa San Antonio, Gustavo Garcia-Siller, yanditse kuri twitter ati: “Mukama, bagirire ikigongwe
 Bifuza kuronka ubuzima bwiza gusumba
” “Kandi,  ukutubahuka guhangana n’impinduka zijanye n’abimukira, vyongeye kwica no gusambura ubuzima”

Abategetsi b’ibihugu indwi  bitunze gusumba ibindi kw’isi (G7) biyemeje gufasha Ukraine “igihe cose bizoba bikenewe”, hari ku musi ugira kabiri w’ikoraniro barimwo mu Budagi
 Mw’itangazo, ibihugu vya G7 bivuga kandi ko Uburusiya butegerezwa guhagarika kuzibira ibifungurwa bubibuza kuva ku bivuko vya Ukraine
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije ibi bihugu yifashishije ubuhinga bwa videwo, umukuru w’igihugu ca Ukraine yateye akamo ibihugu vy’Uburengero ko vyomuha ibindi birwanisho vya rutura
 Abategetsi ba G7 bari mu ngorane yo kutabona ibintu kumwe mu nzira yavyo ku gitero c’Uburusiya kibandanya cunyura ibintu
 Mw’iri tangazo basohoye nijoro ku wa mbere ryarimwo amajambo akomeye, aba bategetsi bavuga bati: “Tuzobandanya dufasha Ukraine mu kuyiha imfashanyo y’amafaranga, y’ubutabazi, ya gisirikare n’imigenderanire, mu gihe cose bizoba ari ngombwa “Turacababajwe kandi tubandanya twiyamiriza igitero c’ubugome, kitagira imvo, kidasiguritse, kandi giteye kubiri n’amategeko kuri Ukraine cakozwe n’Uburusiya bufashijwe na Biélorussie [Belarus]”
 Abategetsi ba G7  - Canada, Ubufaransa, Ubudagi, Ubutaliyano, Ubuyapani, Ubwongereza na Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika – bahambijwe n’intumwa zibiri zo mu Bumwe bwa Bulaya i Bavière/Bavaria mu Budagi
 Ibi biganiro vyo ku rwego rwo hejuru vyabaye mu gihe ingabo z’Uburusiya zongereje akariro mu bitero kuri Ukraine, aho abategetsi bavuga ko inyubakwa y’idandarizo yatewe igisasu ca misire mu gisagara ca Kremenchuk kiri hagati mu gihugu, kigahitana abantu n’imiburiburi cumi, nk’uko bivugwa na buramatari
 Igihe yahamagara mw’ihoteri y’akaroruhore iyi nama yariko iberamwo, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky yasabiye Ukraine ibindi birwanisho vya rutura, anavuga ko yizeye ko intambara ishobora   kuba yarangiye mu mpera z’uno mwaka “imbere y’uko igihe c’ubukonje gitangura”
 Hari amakenga ko igihe c’ubukonje (hiver/winter) aho usanga ibirere ari bibi cane gishoboa kubangamira cane ingabo za Ukraine
 Yasavye kandi ibihugu vy’uburengero ko vyobandanya bitera igitsure Uburusiya mu kubufatira ibindi bihano
 Mw’itangazo rusangi, abategetsi b’ibihugu vya G7 bavuze ko baciyemeje “kugumizaho no kwongereza” ibihano kuri reta ya Perezida Vladimir Putin na Biélorussie imufashe mu mugongo
 Hagiye gufatwa ibihano ku bidandazwa vy’i’ nzahabu n’igitoro bishorwa hanze, “abagirizwa ivyaha vyo mu ntambara” na bo nyene bafatirwe ibihano, nk’uko iri tangazo rusangi ribivuga
 G7 kandi isaba Kremlin ko yorekura imfungurwa zikava ku bivuko vya Ukraine – yongera yagiriza Moscou kwongereza ubwoba bw’ubukene bw’ibifungurwa kw’isi nk’inkurikizi y’iyi ntambara
 Igice kinini c’intete kirumara za Ukraine zategerezwa gushorwa hanze zishobora kuborera mu bubiko mu gihe ingabo z’Uburusiya zikizibiye ibivuko vya Ukraine ku Nyanja Yirabura (Mer Noire/Black Sea)
 Iri tangazo rya G7 rivuga riti: “Turasaba vyihuta Uburusiya ko buhagarika ataco burinze gusaba ibitero ku nyubakwa z’uburimyi n’amabarabara bukareka ivyimburwa bigasohoka ibivuko vya Ukraine”
 Amatohoza ya BBC yatoye ivyemezo vyerekana ko ingabo z’Uburusiya mu turere twa Ukraine zigaruriye zigenda ziba intete hamwe n’ibindi vyimburwa vy’abarimyi
  Mw’ijambo yashikirije muri iri koraniro, umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubwongereza Boris Johnson yabwiye BBC ko ari “ngombwa ko igiciro c’ubwigenge cishurwa" mu gufata mu mugongo Ukraine, kandi ko iyi mfashanyo itegerezwa kubandanya itangwa kugira ngo iki gihugu gisanure ubutunzi bwaco, gishore hanze intete congere gikingire abanyagihugu baco
 Imbere y’aho ejo ku wa mbere, umushikiranganji Johnson yafashwe isanamu ariko ashinyaguriza Vladimir Putin – akunze kwifotoza agatuza kambaye ubusa – abwira abandi bategetsi ko ari ngombwa ko “twereka [Uburusiya] inguvu zacu”
 Mu gihe abategetsi ba G7 bari mu nama yabo ejo ku wa mbere, hari amakuru yasohotse yavuga ko Uburusiya butashoboye kwishura ideni ryabwo ku ncuro ya mbere kuva mu 1998, inyuma yo kunanirwa no kuriha ku gihe imiriyoni 100 z’amadorari y’abanyamerika
 Hagati aho, Kremlin ivuga ko ikibazo atari “ingorane yacu”, kubera aya mafaranga yarishwe mu kwa gatanu, ariko akazibirwa n’ibihano vy’Uburengero

Uwigeze gutwara umudari wa olempike incuro zibiri n'uwo ihiganwa ry'isi yose incuro zitatu, Caster Semenya, yise abategetsi ba Afrika muvyo kwinonora imitsi, ba "niryo" kuba barananiwe guhagarara bakagwanira abanonotsi b'abapfasoni bahanganye n'ikibazo co gukurwa mu mahiganwa
 Uwo munonotsi w'imyaka 31  yarakuwe ku rutonde rw'abahiganwa ku metero akunda gusiganwako 800 hisunzwe amategeko  agenga inkabuzo ya "testostérone" umuntu aba afise mu mubiri, y'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryo kwinonora imitsi mu 2019
 Abanonotsi bafise inkabuzo nyinshi za "testostérone" basabwa gukoresha umuti mu kuzigabanya kugira bashobore guhiganwa ku metero ziri hagati ya 400 na 1500
 Semenya yagize ati: "Nibaza ko, kuri uyu musi, dufise abategetsi ba 'niryo'"
 "Kuri uyu mugabane, abantu baranumye
 Sintahura igituma batavuga
 Ntibagwanira abanonotsi babo
 "Mutegerezwa guseruka mugakora, mukagwanira abanonotsi banyu, gutyo abanonotsi ba Afrika bazoba beza cane
 Ubu uko bimeze birababaje
" Igihe BBC Sport Africa yabaza Maboum Kalkaba, prezida w'urunani rw'amashirahamwe yo kwinonora imitsi muri Afrika (CAA), ivyerekeye ivyo Semanya avuga, n'uko abategetsi barongoye ishirahamwe ryo kwinonora imitsi muri Afrika bakoreye ibikwiye abo barongoye, yishuye ati: "Nimundeke, nta nyishu mfise"
 Abanonotsi benshi bo muri Afrika barakozweko n'iyo ngingo, harimwo umunonotsi w'umurundikazi yatahukanye umudari w'ifeza mu nkino za olempike, Francine Niyonsaba, hamwe na mugenzi we wo muri Kenya bahiganwa ku metero 800
 Mu mwaka uheze, abayabaga babiri bo muri Namibia, Christine Mboma na Beatrice Masilingi, barahatiwe kuva mw'ihiganwa rya metero 400, imbere y'imisi mike ngo habe inkino za olempike za Tokyo inyuma yo kumenyeshwa ko bafise urugero runini rw'inkabuzo za testostérone
 Bompi Mboma na Masilingi batinze bahiganwa mu metero 200 mu Buyapani, aho Mboma yatahukanye umudari w'ifeza wa mbere wa olempike w'ico gihugu
 Ariko Semenya, ubu ahiganwa ku metero 5000, yaranebaguye ingene abategetsi b'ishirahamwe rya Afrika riraba abanonotsi bitwaye kuri ico kibazo c'abo bayabaga co kimwe n'"agacerere" ku ngingo yafashwe yo kubabuza guhiganwa muri rusangi
 Uwo munye Afrika y'epfo yagize ati: "Igihe nari mfise imyaka 18, sinashobora kuvuga
 Ubu ndakuze bikwiye, ndashobora kuvuga
 "Nimwiyumvire ivyaciye mu mitwe y'iyo miyabaga
 Nta co bashobora gukora, ariko abategetsi bariyicariye gusa binezerererwa gusa n'uturusho bafise, mu bibanza biberamwo amanama
 Umuyobozi mukuru wa CAA, Lamine Faty yavuze ko Semenya "afise uburenganzira bwo gushikiriza ivyo yiyumvira" kandi ko ibibazo ku ngingo zatumye bakurwa mw'ihiganwa vyashikirijwe n'iryo shirahamwe "kera cane" kandi ko vyaganiriweko mu misi ya vuba mu kanama ka CAA  mu nama yabereye muri Ile Maurice
 Impari kw'itorwa ry'abagore bagira uruhara muri siporo zabaye nyinhsi, na cane cane zikaba zashimikiye ku banonotsi bameze nk'abagabo kandi ari abakobwa
 Mu ndwi iheze, prezida w'ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ryo kwinonora imitsi, Seb Coe, yavuze ko iryo shirahamwe rishobora gukurikizako igisata co kwoga, mu kubuza abagore biyumva nk'abagabo kuja mw'ihiganwa, avuga ashimitse ko "kutarenganya bidashobora guharirwako"
 Yabwiye BBC Sport ati: "Tubandanya twiga, tugira ubushakashatsi ku bwinshi bw'inkabuzo ya testostérone ko ari kimwe mu bituma umuntu akomera gusumba , tukaba twarategekanije ibiganiro ku mategeko yacu mu kanama kacu mu mpera y'umwaka
" Semenya, yatwaye umudari w'inzahabu ku metero 800 mu myaka ya 2012 na 2016 mu nkino za olempike, yari yunguruje ku ngingo zafashwe n'ishirahamwe ry'abanonotsi kw'isi, ariko aratsindwa muri sentare ica imanza z'inkino mu 2019
 Yaratsinzwe kandi muri sentare y'iyungururizo no muri sentare ntahinyuzwa y'Ubuswise mu mwaka wakurikiye, imbere yo kwitura sentare ya Buraya ijejwe agateka ka zina muntu aho urwo rubanza rutarumvirizwa
 Yagize ati: "Ntituzigera duhagarika uru rugamba
" "Ubu ibi ntibiraba jewe gusa, biraba abana bakiri bato ubu bariko baravuka bazohangana n'iki kibazo
 "Hari abana benshi bipfuza guhiganwa ku metero 400, 800 na 1500, ariko ntibashobora kubemerera
 Bavuga ko siporo ari iya bose, ariko ubu si iya bose
"
Prezida wa Ukraine Volodimyr Zelensky yasavye abategetsi b’ibihugu indwi vya  mbere bikize kw’isi bihurikiye mu mugwu G7 “kutagabanya  kwotsa igitutu Uburusiya  no kubandanya barunda ingingo z’ibihano “ziremereye”  ku Burusiya, nk’uko bivugwa n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP
 Zelensky yabivugiye mw’ijambo yashikirije ku buryo bwa video-link, ku munsi ugira kabiri w’inama y’iminsi itatu y’abakuru ba G7
 Yongeye gusaba ko Ukraine ihabwa ibindi bigwanisho biremereye hamwe n’ivyo kwikingira  ibitero vy’indege kugira Ukraine yihagarareko mu gihe Uburusiya bukomeje kuyigabako ibitero vya misire
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubudagi Olaf Scholz avuga ko G7 “izobandanya kwongereza igitutu kuri Putin”
 Zelensky yifuza ko intanbara irangira imbere y’uko uyu mwaka uhera
\nUmukuru wa Ukraine yabwiye abategetsi ba G7 ko ashaka ko intambara yo muri Ukraine irangira imbere y’uko igihe c’imbeho (winter/hiver)  gitangura, ku bwa Reuters
 Zelensky yavuze ko  ingene hazoboba hameze ku rugamba bitazokworohera ingabo ziwe kwivuna, aca asaba abategetsi ba  G7 gukora ibishoboka vyose kugira intambra irangire  imbere y’uko umwaka uhera, nk’uko AFP ibivuga ikurikije isoko ryayo
 Muri iyo nama  ya G7 iriko irabera  Elmau Castle muri  Kruen mu Budagi, Zelensky yasavye kandi imfashanyo yo gusubira kwubaka igihugu, ibigwanishjo vyo kwirinda ibitero vy’indege, ubufasha bw’ingene Ukraine yoshora intete zayo hamwe n’uburyo bwo kuyizera umutekano
 Abategetsi ba G7 bariko barihweza ibihano bishasha bofatira Uburusiya kugirango bakongataze inguvu za Putin mu ntambara
 Intumbero n'ukugira bereke Putin ko ibihugu vy’uburengerazuba bitariko birahesha , nk’uko bivugwa n’umunyamakuru akurkirana ivy'imigenderanire (diplomacie) James Landale
 Ku wa mungu, Ubwongereza, Amerika, Canada n'Ubuyapani vyavuze ko bigiye kubuza kugura inzahabu z'Uburusiya kugira babuze Moscou kuronka uburyo bwo gushira mu ntambara muri Ukraine
 Umukuru wa Amerika Joe Biden yavuze ko ibindi bihugu vya G7 - Ubudagi, Ubufaransa n'Ubutaliyano - navyo bizohagarika kugura izo nzahabu
 Gushora inzahabu vyinjirije Uburusiya miriyaridi 15
4 z'ama dorari mu 2021, Ubwongereza bukavuga ko ubu inzahabu zarushirije kugira ikibanza gikomeye kuko ba ruhebwa mu gutunga bihutira kugura inzahabu kugira birinde ibihano
 Ibihugu vya G7 biriko biraraba kandi ingene vyoshinga igiciro ntarengwa ku bitoro vy'Uburusiya, nk'uko bivugwa ko vyashikirijwe n'umutegetsi wo muri Amerika
 Uwo mutegetsi asubirwamwo na AFP ko yavuze ati: "Turacariko turaheraheza ibiganiro n'abandi bo muri G7 kugira duheraheze iyo nteguro, ariko turi hafi yo gushika aho abategetsi ba G7 bafata ingingo yo gutegeka abashikiranganji babijejwe gushiraho indinganizo yo gushinga igiciro ntarengwa c'ibitoro vy'Uburusiya"
 Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje kandi ibihano bishasha ku gisata co kivuna c'Uburusiya, nk'uko bivugwa na AFP
 Ibiro vy'umukuru w'igihugu White House vyavuze ko " abategetsi ba G7 bazoja ku murongo umwe hanyuma bongereze ibihano bizorushirizaho kubuza Uburusiya kuronka ubuhinga bw'ibihugu vyo mu burengerazuba bushobora gushigikira inganda z'ibigwanisho z'Uburusiya
 Amerika izorushirizaho kandi kugabanya ubushobozi bw'Uburusiya bwo gusubiriza ibikoresho vya gisirikare bumaze gutakaza mu ntambara
 Abategetsi ba G7 bivugwa kandi ko bumvikanye ko amafaranga ava ku makori yongerejwe ku bicuruzwa vy'Uburusiya yohabwa Ukraine, ku bwa AFP isubiramwo ivyavuzwe n'ibiro vy'umukuru wa Amerika
 Umutegetsi w'umunyamerika yavuze ko abategetsi ba G7 bazorondera ububasha bwo gukoresha amafaranga yose yongerejwe ku bicuruzwa vy'Uburusiya mu mfashanyo zihabwa Ukraine kugira Uburusiya abe aribwo buriha intambwara bwateje bwo nyene

Na Gordon Corera, Umunyamakuru ashikiriza amakuru y'umutekano, BBC News Abategetsi b’Ubuholande bavuga ko maneko w’umurusiya yari yiyoberanije ku rugero rwo hejuru yagerageje gucengetera muri Sentare Mpuzamakungu mpanavyaha y’i La Haye/ The Hague
 Uyu mugabo yakoresha izina rya Viktor Muller Ferreira yigize umunya-Brezili ariko yankirwa kwinjira igihe yari ashitse kugira ngo atangure akazi mu Buholande
 Abategetsi bavuga ko izina ryiwe nyaryo ari Sergey Vladimirovich Cherkasov, kandi ko ari maneko wa GRU – urwego rw’igendereza rya gisirikare rw’Uburusiya
 Uyu mugabo avugwa ko yamaze imyaka itari mike agerageza kwubaka umwidondoro w’’ukwiyoberanya, imbere y’uko asaba ikibanza muri CPI i La Haye/The Hague kugira akore imyimenyerezo (stage/internship)
 Igisata c’Ubuholande kijejwe igendereza , AIVD, kivuga ko iyo aramuka ashoboye kuronka ico kibanza hanyuma agacengetera muri iyi sentare, yari kwonona ibitari bike
 Mw’itangazo casohoye, ik igisata cavuze kiti: “Ivyo uyu mukozi w’igendereza yari kwonona vyari kuba vyinshi”
 Viktor Muller Ferreira yari azwi nk’umunya-Brezili yitaho kumenya ibijanye n’imigenderanire mpuzamakungu
 Ariko mu vyo ukuri, nk’uko AIVD ibivuga, yari maneko adasanzwe w’Uburusiya azwi “nk’uwutemewe n’amategeko”
 Urwego rujejwe igendereza rurakoresha aya majambo kugira rubatandukanye na ba maneko “b’ukuri” bagenda biyita ko ari abakozi bo mu biro vy’ubuserukizi
 Ibihugu vyinshi birakoresha ba maneko bigira abantu basanzwe ariko Uburusiya bufise uburambe mu gukoresha ba maneko mu buryo butemewe n’amategeko babanje gufata ubwenegihugu bw’ibindi bihugu
 Aba ba maneko b’ubu bwoko bakunze kwigira abanyamerika, abongereza, abanya-Canada canke – nk’uyu Ferreira – abanya-Brezili kugira ngo biborohere kuzunguruka mu turere tutokworohera Abarusiya bigatuma badashobora kuhakorera
 AIVD yasohoye igitabo gitangaje kizwi ko canditswe na Cherkasov mu myaka ya 2010, ari naho avuga uwidondoro wiwe w’ukwiyoberanya
 Iki gitabo gitangura kiti: “Nitwa Viktor Muller Ferreira”
 Itorwa ry’iki gitabo ryerekana urugero kanaka ry’urwangara rw’uyu maneko
 Ku mpapuro zine za mbere asigura umuryango wiwe
 Umurongo umwe uvuga uku: “Dawe yabonetse ko yari umuntu mwiza kandi w’intungane, ariko nagiye gutangara menye ko ari we yishe mama na senge kandi ari we abazwa ingorane n’agasuzuguro naciyemwo mu buzima bwanje”
 Mu nyuma yerekana ingene vyabaye ngombwa ko agenda miuri Irlande ku maziko ya se wiwe
 Bishobora gufata imyaka iri hagati y’itanu na cumi kugira ngo maneko atemewe n’amategeko yigishwe ashoboye kwiyoberanya
 Kubera ari ibintu bitoroshe, abantu nk’aba bazwi ko ari bake cane – kumbure bashobora kuba badashika 30 muri GRU, nk’uko ibihugu vy’uburengero bivyibaza
 Igendereza ry'Uburusiya rimaze imyaka myinshi rigerageza gucengetera muri CPI, Ferreira akaba azwi ko yatanguye kugerageza gusaba ikibanza  mu mwaka uheze
 Kuva Uburusiya butanguje igitero kuri Ukraine, CPI yabaye ihangiro nyamukuru
 Ku wa 03 z’ukwa gatatu, umushikirizamanza mukuru wa CPI yatanguje amatohoza ku vyaha vyo mu ntambara n’ivyaha vyo guhohotera kiremwamuntu muri Ukraine
 CPI isanzwe isanzwe yakira abantu bagera ku 200 bahakorera imyimenyerezo badahembwa, ibi bikaba akaryo ko “kumenya ingene CPI ikora, no gushira mu bikorwa ivyo baba barize bahagarikiwe n’ababifisemwo uburambe”
 Iyo aronka aya mahirwe, yari kuharonkera amakuru menshi
 Mw’itangazo yasohoye, AIVD ivuga iti: “Iyo uyu maneko ashobora kuronka amahirwe yo gutangura akazi muri CPI, yari gushobora kwegeranya amakuru y’igendereza mbere akarondera n’abamuha amakuru, kandi agashobora no kwinjira mu mashini nyabwonko za CPI”
 “Aha rero yari gushobora kuharonkera amakuru akomeye asanzwe aronderwa n’igendereza rya GRU”
 Kurondera akazi muri CPI nka maneko yiyoberanije harimwo imitego myinshi, ariko biboneka ko umwe mu bakuru biwe i Moscou babonye ko vyari ngombwa
 Aba ba maneko batazwi baragoye guhinyura – nta wuzi nimba yoba yagiye guhinyurwa na CPI – mu gihe abategetsi b’Ubuholande batavuze ingene bamutoye
 Imbuga hwaniro zihwejwe na BBC zizwi ko ari iza Ferreira zerekana ko afise urutonde runini cane rw’abagenzi – harimwo igitigiri c’abanyeshure mvamakungu bo kuri kaminuza zibiri asa n’uwizeko – Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins muri Amerika hamwe na Trinity College, i  Dublin muri Irlande
 Abo bagenzi biwe bose bahavuye bakora mu bisata bitandukanye hose, haba mu mabanki, mu mashirahamwe y’abahinga no mu bigo vya reta i Washington DC
 Ariko ntibigeze baca n’ikanda ko yari maneko w’Uburusiya
 Umwe mu bigisha yamwigishije yabwiye BBC ati: “Yari afise imvugo imeze ukuntu
 Ariko ntiyari iy’ikirusiya”
 Ferreira azwi ko yatanguye gusaba ikibanza muri CPI mu ntango z’ukw’icenda 2020 ariko ntiyashoka yishurwa kubera Covid
 Igihe kimwe yavuze ati: “Brezili ntiserukiwe muri CPI, rero aka gashobora kuba akaryo kuri jewe”
 Umwidondoro umwe werekana ko Ferreira yimukiye i Washington DC muri Myandagaro (8) umwaka wa 2018 kandi inzandiko zerekana ko yahejeje ivyigwa vyiwe kuri Johns Hopkins mu 2020
 Inyandiko zo ku mbuga hwaniro zerekana uruvangatirane rw’ivyiyumviro harimwo n’ibinegura bukebuke Uburusiya, ibi bigafatwa ko yariko abandanya gaerageza kwiyoberanya gusumba
 Hariho n’aho mbere n’aho asa n’uwacishije kuri konte yiwe y’imbuga hwaniro inkuru y’urubuga rwa Bellingcat ivuga imyidondoro y’ububeshi ikoreshwa na GRU yafashwe, ikintu kidasanzwe ku muntu we nyene ubwiwe yagirizwa ko ari maneko yiyoberanije wa GRU
 Ubu rero inyuma y’aho ahinyukiye, kazoza kiwe nka maneko yiyoberanije kiagiye kurangira

