Uburusiya bugiye kurungikira incuti yabwo Biélorussie/Belarus misire za nikleyeri zirasa hafi mu mezi ari imbere, nk’uko Perezida Vladimir Putin abivuga
 Avuga ko ibigwanisho vya Iskander-M bishobora kurekura ubwoko butandukanye bwa misire harimwo n’iza nikleyeri
 Ibi birwanisho bishobora kurasa ibisasu gushika ku birometero 500
 Icuka kibi hagati y’Uburusiya n’Uburengero cariyongereye cane, inyuma y’ingingo ya Perezida Putin yo gutera Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2)
 Kuva ico gihe, Perezida Putin amaze kuvuga kenshi ku vyerekeye ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri, ivyo bamwe bafata ko ari ukugabisha ibihugu vy’Uburengero kugira ntivyite muri iyi ntambara
 Avugira mu gisagara ca St Petersburg, Perezida Putin yavuze ko Uburusiya bugiye guhindura indege za Biélorussie SU-25 kugira ngo zishobore kwikorera ibirwanisho ruhonyanganda vya nikleyeri nk’uko vyasabwe na Perezida Lukashenko
 Hagati aho, hari ibibombe bitari bike vyaturikiye ku mugwa mukuru Kyiv mu gatondo ko kuri uyu wa Mungu, nk’uko bivugwa n’umukuru w’iki gisagara Vitali Klitschko
 Yongerako ati: “Za rusehabaniha n’abajejwe ubutabazi bahashitse, kandi ibikorwa vyo gutabara no guhungisha abantu birabandanya mu nyubakwa zibiri”
 Itororokanirizo ry’amakuru AFP rivuga ko inyubakwa isanzwe ituwemwo n’abantu yatewe
 Ejo ku wa gatandatu,Ukraine yatangaje ko ingabo z’Uburusiya “zigaruriye” igisagara gikomeye ca Severodonetsk cose inyuma y’amayinga kirangwamwo intambara z’urutavanako
 Ukwigarurira iki gisagara bisigura ko ubu Uburusiya bugenzura hafi intara yose ya Luhansk n’igice kinini ca Donesk – intara zibiri zigize akarere ka Donbas karangwamwo amahinguriro
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu buryo bwa videwo mu masaha yitereye nijoro ku wa gatandatu, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine yiyemeje ko ategerezwa kwisubiza “ibisagara vyacu vyose” vyigaruriwe n’Uburusiya
 Ariko yavuze ko intambara n’Uburusiya yinjiye mu gihe kigoye kandi kibabaje, ko atazi ingene ibizokwononekara bizongana
 Ku wa gatanu mw’ijoro, Uburusiya bwarateye ibisasu vya misire vyinshi mu turere turi mu buraruko no mu burengero bwa Ukraine
 N’imiburiburi abantu batatu barishwe abandi nabo bakaba bashobora kuba baguweko n’ibihomoka mu gisagara ca Sarny kiri mu burengero bwa Kyiv, nk’uko bivugwa n’umutegetsi w’akarere
 Bimwe muri vya muzinga vyatewe biva muri Biélorussie, nk’uko Ukraine ibivuga
 Biélorussie yifatanije n’Uburusiya ariko igisirikare cayo ntikirwana ku mugaragaro muri iyi ntambara
 Igisata ca Ukraine kijejwe igendereza kivuga ko ibi bitero vya misire biri mu twigoro twa Kremlin two kwinjiza Biélorussie muri ino ntambara
 Ifatwa rya Severodonetsk ribaye hasigaye indwi imwe ngo ibihugu vy’Uburengero bitangure umubonano, aho Perezida Joe Biden wa Amerika yitezwe mu Budagi mu nama ihuza ibihugu bitunze gusumba ibindi bihurikiye mu citwa G7, ikazokurikirwa n’ibiganiro vya OTAN/NATO
 Mu mezi make aheze, iri huriro ry’ibihugu vy’Uburengero ryarerekanye ibimenyetso vyo kudebukirwa  ariko ku wa gatandatu umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubwongereza yavuze ko ari ngombwa ko Ukraine itsinda iyi ntambara n’Uburusiya
 Ati: “Ubu si igihe co guheberana Ukraine”
 Kuri uno wa Mungu, umukuru w’igihugu ca Indonesia Joko Widodo, akaba yitezwe muri iyi nama ya G7, avuga ko azosaba abategetsi ba Ukraine n’Uburusiya gusubira mu biganiro
 Muri ino nama yo ku wa gatandatu yacishijwe ku mboneshakure na mugenziwe wa Biélorussie Alexander Lukashenko i St Petersburg,  Putin yavuze ati: “Twafashe ingingo: mu mezi make ari imbere, tugiye guha Biélorussie misire za Iskander-M”
 Yavuze ko ibijanye n’ingene tuzobitanga bizokwigwa n’ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi b’ibi bihugu vyompi
 Misire za Iskander ziramaze gushikanwa i Kaliningrad, akarere kegukira Uburusiya kari mu karere ka Baltique hagati y’ibihugu vya OTAN Lithuania na Pologne
 Aba bakuru b’ibihugu babiri baraganiriye ku ngingo ya Lithuania yo kubuza ibidandazwa bimwe bimwe kwinjira no gusohoka biva i Kaliningrad – ingingo yashavuje cane Moscou
 Umukuru w’igihugu ca Biélorussie avuga ko ingingo ya Lithuania ari “nk’ugutangaza intambara” kandi ko “idashobora kwihanganirwa”
 Ubutare bw’ivyuma n’ibindi bidandazwa vy’Uburusiya vyarafatiwe ibihano n’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya kubera igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine
 Lithuania ivuga ko ingingo zayo zigira inkurikizi ku bidandazwa bisanzwe vy’Uburusiya ku rugero rwa 1% gusa, AGAHAKANA amajambo avugwa n’Uburusiya ko Kaliningrad “yazibiwe”

