Amamiriyoni y'abagore muri Reta Zunze Ubunmwe za Amerika bagiye gutakaza uburenganzira bahabwa n'ibwirizwashingiro bwo gukoroza inda, inyuma y'aho sentare nkuru y'ico gihugu ikuriyeho ingingo yari imaze imyaka 50, izwi nka Roe V Wade
 Iyi ngingo ya sentare yugururiye inzira intara ku giti cazo yo guhagarika ubu burenganzira
 Igice cazo zitezwe gushiraho ayandi mategeko y'inzitizi canke guhagarika burundu ubu burenganzira
 Cumi na zitatu muri zo zari zamaze kwemeza icitwa amategeko mbarutso (trigger laws) abuza ugukoroza inda
 Perezida Joe Biden avuga ko iyi ngingo ari  "ukwihenda gukomeye", aca atera akamo intara ko zoshiraho amategeko yemerera ababishaka gukoroza inda
 Inyuma y'iyi ngingo ya sentare nkuru y'igihugu, vyitezwe ko abagore bababa imiriyoni 36 bari mu myaka yo kuvyara batakaza ubu burenganzira, nk'uko biri mu cegeranyo c'ishirahamwe Planned Parenthood rifasha gukoroza inda
 Abanywanyi b'impande zompi biyegeranirije imbere y'iyi sentare mu myiyerekano, igipolisi kikaba ari co cabatandukanije
 Umwe mu barwanya ugukoroza inda yabwiye BBC ko yari "anezerewe cane" mu gihe we na bagenziwe bariko bishimira iyi ngingo
 Uyu mupfasoni ati:  "Kugira iki kintu itegeko y'igihugu vyonyene ntibihagije
 Gushigikira ko abantu bagira uburenganzira bwo kubaho bisigura ko ata muntu ashobora kwiyumvira gukorora inda"
 Ku rundi ruhande, abashigikiye ko abantu bihitiramwo ugukoroza inda canke kuyitwara gushika ivuke bariyamiriza iyi ngingo, bakavuga ko "itemewe" kandi ko ari iyo "agahotoro"
 Umunyamakuru wa BBC Samantha Granville yari kw'ivuriro rikorora inda mu karere ka Little Rock muri Arkansas avuga ko igihe iyi ngingo yasohoka, imiryango yo mu cumba c'abarwayi yaciye yugarwa, yumva amajwi y'abantu bapfunagira imbere y'uko asabwa gusohoka
 Iyi ntara iri mu zemeje itegeko mbarutso
 Igihe iri tegeko ryiswe Roe v Wade rishingwa mu 1973, Sentare Nkuru yakoze amatora, indwi bararyemeza babiri bararihakana, rikaba ryavuga ko uburenganzira bw'umugore bwo gukoroza inda bukingiwe n'ibwirizwashingiro rya Amerika
 Iri tegeko ryahaye abagore b'amanyamerikakazi uburenganzira bwose bwo gukoroza inda mu gihe ikiri mu mezi atatu ya mbere, ariko ryemeza ko hashobora gushiraho inzitizi (restrictions) mu gice ca kabiri c'imbanyi, n'amategeko yo kubibuza burundu mu gice ca gatatu
 Ariko mu myaka mirongo kuva ico gihe, amategeko abuza gukoroza inda yagiye afatwa mu ntara zirenga cumi
 Muri ino ngingo ya kino gihe, Sentare nkuru yihweje urubanza rumwe, ruzwi nka Dobbs v Jackson Women's Health Organization, ku ngingo ya  Mississippi yo kubuza ugukorora inda imaze amayinga 15
 Mu ngingo ishigikira iyi ntara, iyi sentare igizwe ahanini n'abashira imbere ivyiyumviro vya kera (Conservateurs/Convervative) yahagaritse ubu burenganzira bwo gukoroza inda butangwa n'ibwirizwashingiro
 Abacamanza batanu bashigikiye cane iyi ngingo: Samuel Alito, Clarence Thomas, Neil Gorsuch, Brett Kavanaugh na Amy Coney Barrett
 Umukuru w'iyi sentare John Roberts yanditse iciyumviro avuga ko, n'aho yashigikiye ingingo ya Mississipi ibuza gukorora inda, ntiyari kurenza aho
 Abacamanza batatu banse ingingo ya benshi  - Stephen Breyer, Sonia Sotomayor na  Elena Kagan - banditse bavuga ko bakoze uko  "n'umubabaro - kuri ino sentare, ariko cane cane, ku mamiriyoni menshi y'abanyamerikakazi batakaje uburenganzira bwabo bukomeye bahabwa n'ibwirizwashingiro"
 Iyi ngingo yaraye ifashwe ejo ku wa gatanu ni ingingo ivuguruza iyo yo nyene yari yafashe - ibidakunze kwibonekeza - kandi ishobora kuba intandaro y'intambara za poritike zicanishijemwo iki gihugu
 Mu ntara aho abahigikiye ugukoroza inda n'abatabishigikiye basa n'abangana  - izi ni nka Pennsylvania, Michigan na Wisconsin - bishobora kubanza guca mu matora kugira ngo iyi ingingo ije mu ngiro
 Mu zindi ntara, iyi ngingo ishobora gutuma havyuka intambara nshasha z'amategeko, harimwo no kwemeza canke guhakana nimba abantu ku giti cabo bashobora kuva mu ntara bakaja gukoroza inda mu zindi zitanga ubu burenganzira, canke bagatumako imiti bakoresheje uburyo bwa posita (mail)
 Igihe yiyamiriza iyi ngingo ya sentare nkuru y'igihugu, Perezida Biden yabwiye abagore bo mu ntara zidatanga ubu burenganzira ko bofata ingendo bakaja mu ntara zibutanga
 Ba buramatari b'aba Democrats mu ntara zitari nke harimwo nka California, New Mexico na Michigan, bamaze gutangaza ko bategura zo gushiramwo ingingo zitanga uburenganzira bwo gukoroza inda mu mabwirizwashingiro yazo
 Buramatari wa Mississippi Tate Reeves yaciye yihutira gushigikira iyi ngingo, aho avuga ko intara yiwe "yarongoye igihugu kwiganzura kimwe mu bigize akarenganyo gakomeye mu mateko y'igihugu cacu"
 Mike Pence yahoze ari icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu, akaba kuva kera yamye  arwanya ingingo Roe v Wade, yasavye abashigikiye iyi ngingo ya Sentare kubandanya urugamba gushika "agaciro k'ubuzima" gakingiwe n'amategeko mu ntara zose
 Ku rundi ruhande, umukuru w'inama nshingamateka, umu Democrat Nancy Pelosi yavuze ko "iyi sentare nkuru yiganjemwo aba Repubulika" yashitse ku ntumbero ikomeye y'umwijima" y'uwu mugambwe
 Yanditse ati: "Abanyamerikakazi uno musi bafise uburenganzira buke ugereranije na ba nyina babo
 "Iyi ngingo y'ubugome ni agahomerabunwa kandi ni incamugongo"
 Ihinduka ry'iyi ngingo yari imaze igihe kitari gito yatumye havyuka ubwoba ko n'izindi ngingo zitanga ubundi burenganzira zafashwe na sentare nkuru y'igihugu muri kahise zishobora guhura n'ibibazo
 Umucamanza Clarence Thomas, mu ciyumviro ciwe yashikirije, yanditse ati: "Muri kazoza, twari dukwiye kuzokwihweza neza ingingo zagiye zifatwa n'iyi sentare, harimwo Griswold, Lawrence, na Obergefell" - aha akaba yashaka kuvuga ku ngingo zikomeye zitatu zo muri kahise, nk'uko bikurikirana, ku burenganzira bwo kubuza imbanyi umuntu atipfuza (contraception), gufuta amategeko abuza imibonano mpuzabitsina yo mu kibuno (sodomie/sodomy ), hamwe n'ayatanga uburenganzira bwo kwubakana ku bantu basangiye igitsina

Inama y'abakuru b'ibihugu bihurikiye mw'ishirahamwe ry'abakoresha ururimi rw'icongereza, Commonwealth, yatanguye icese i Kigali ku mugwa mukuru w'Urwanda
 Prezida Paul Kagame agiye kurongora uwo mugwi w'ibihugu 54 - birimwo ica gatatu c'abantu bose baba kw'isi, yavuze ko indangagaciro ari zo ziranga abagize iryo shirahamwe
 Ivyo birimwo intwaro ibereye, kwubahiriza amategeko n'agateka ka zina muntu
 Kwakira iyo nama vyatumye haba abanebagura reta yiwe ku vyo imaze gushikako ku gateka ka zina muntu
 Yabwiye ishengero ryitavye iyo nama ati: "Igihe cose tuzonanirwa, tuzotora inyishu biciye mu mwumvikano n'ibiganiro
 N'ugushigikirana hagati yacu no gutera intambwe imbere turi kumwe"
 Yavuze ko igihugu ciwe kimaze kugira urugendo rurerure kuva habaye jenoside mu 1994, aho abantu barenga 800
000 bishwe
 Yongeyeko  ati: "Ariko uyu musi turi abantu bahindutse ku mutima, ku mushaha no ku mubiri
" Igice kinini c'abagize ishirahamwe Commonwealth kigizwe n'ibihugu vyahoze bikoronijwe n'Ubwongereza, ariko hagiye hiyongeramwo ibindi harimwo n'Urwanda
 Prezida Kagame yavuze ko kuja muri iryo shirahamwe vyari bifise intumbero y'uko "abanyagihugu bacu baja hamwe, biyumvanamwo hanyuma bakaraba imbere muri kazoza"
 Gabon - igihugu cahoze gikoronijwe n'Ubufaransa - citeze kwemererwa kwinjira muri iryo shirahamwe muri iyi nama

Inyuma y'icegeranyo gishira ahagaragara ubusuma bw'ama miriyaridi y'amadolari mu kigega ca reta ya Afrika y'epfo ku ntwaro y'uwamubanjirije, prezida Cyril Ramaphosa yariyemeje ko "ivyo bitazosubira kuba 
" Ariko abanye Afrika y'epfo ntibemera ko hari icigwa bakuyemwo
 Barababajwe no kuba amahera yibwe yari gukoreshwa mu bisata vy'amagara y'abantu n'uburezi muri ico gihugu
 Ayo matohoza akomeye ku giturire co ku ntwaro ya prezida Jacob Zuma yerekanye ingene nk'ibisata vyose vya reta vyanigiwe mu menshi, birononwa n'abategetsi ba ANC  (African National Congress), uri ku butegetsi kuva mu 1994 harangiye intwaro y'abazungu bari ku rushi
 Iki cegeranyo cagiriza ahanini uwo mugambwe
 Prezida Ramaphosa ubwiwe yabwiwe n'ako kanama karongowe n'umucamanza, ko atakoze ibikwiye mu gukumira ubwo busuma igihe yari icegera ca Zuma
 Impapuro zirenga 5
000, akanama Zondo - kiswe izina ry'umucamanza wo mu rwego rwo hejuru akarongoye - karerekana ido n'ido ry'ingene ubutunzi bwa reta bwibwe
 Kiranerekana ingene abagwizatunga bavukana bo mu muryango wa Gupta, bagerageje kugira uruhara mu ngingo za politike n'ubutunzi mu ntumbero yiswe  "kwigarurira reta"
 Zuma yirukanywe ku butegetsi mu 2018 yagirizwa igiturire caguma congerekana, hanyuma Ramaphosa aca afata ubutegetsi yiyemeje guhanagura ivyo vyose
 Igice ca nyuma c'ico cegeranyo c'akanama ka Zondo cashikirijwe ku musi wa gatatu
 Prezida akaba yavuze ko ivyo babonye ari "iceyi kuri demokrasi yacu kandi vyahonyanze uburenganzira bw'abanye Afrika y'Epfo bose
" Ariko bimwe muvyo ico cegeranyo casozerereyeko ni gusigira ibibazo prezida ahari ubu ategerezwa kwishura vyerekeye impamvu vyabaye arorera
 Ico cegeranyo kigira kiti: "Hari inkuru nyinshi zifise ifatiro zamenyekanye (


) zashobora kumutuma agira amatohoza akanafata n'ingingo kuri bimwe bivugwa bikomeye
 "Nk'icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu, yari afise ububasha bwo kubikora
" Mu ntango ayo matohoza yategerezwa kuba mu misi 180, ariko ukurengukisha abantu vyatwaye imisi 400 aho ivyabona 300 vyabajijwe
 Ico gikorwa cose catwaye imyaka ine
 Ivyemezo vyarerekanye ingene abategetsi ba ANC, harimwo abashikiranganji b'ubu n'abakera bagiye canke bafashije mu busuma  vyatumye igihugu gihomba amahera menshi
 Muri ivyo harimwo kubuza gukora igisata kijejwe gutoza amakori mu gihugu, gupfukama mu nda ishirahamwe ry'indege South Africa Airways, kwiba amahera mu gisata kijejwe ingendo za gariyamoshi muri ico gihugu no mu kwivanga mu biraba ikinyamakuru ca reta, SABC
 Igisata kijejwe iperereza na co nyene caragabanuwe inguvu mu kugena abakozi bo mu rwego rwo hejuru babujije ko haba amatohoza babisabwe na Zuma n'abandi bantu bifatwa ko bamwegereye

Umuvugizi wa reta ya Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo avuga ko Urwanda rukwiye gufata umugwi witwaje ibigwanisho wa M23 co kimwe na FDLR, yompi ikagwanywa nk’inkozi z’ikibi zihungabanya ‘’umutekano w’Urwanda n’uwa Congo”
 Congo yagiriza Urwanda gushigikira M23 Kinshasa isigaye yita ‘’umugwi w’iterabwoba’
 Urwanda rurahakana  gufasha uwo mugwi uvuga ko ata ”n’urushinge” uhabwa na Kigali
 Mu kiganiro cihariye na BBC Gahuzamiryango, Patrick Muyaya -umushikiranganji ajejwe kumenyesha amakuru muri reta ya Congo akaba n'umuvugizi wayo - yavuze ko n’aho ubu icuka ari kibi cane mu migenderanire hagati ya Congo n’Urwanda, amayira yo kuvugana akihari
 Ati: ”Mwomenya ko uwuserukira Urwanda atawe twirukanye,  dushobora kubandanya tuvugana kugira tugarukane amahoro
 ”Ariko igiteregerezwa kubanza kuba  n’uko Urwanda ruhagarika gufasha M23,  kandi ko M23 co kimwe na FDRLR itegerezwa kurwanywa nk’imigwi y’inkozi z’ikibi uhungabanya umutekano w’Urwanda n’umutekano wa Congo”
 Muyaya avuga ko bafise ivyemezo vyinshi vy’uko ingabo z’Urwanda zajabutse ku butaka bwa Congo gufasha M23
 Muri ivyo, avuga abasirikare babiri b’Urwanda yemeza ko bafatiwe ku birometero 25 imbere ku butaka bwa Congo
 Urwanda rwo rwavuze ko abo basirikare banyurujwe n’abagwanyi ba FDLR babakuye ku butaka bw’Urwanda
 Umuvugizi wa Congo yemeza kandi ko Monusco, ingabo za ONU zikorana n’ingabo za Congo, ifise ivyemezo vyinshi
 Yemeza kandi ko hari amafoto n’ama-video yafashwe n’indege zitagira abadereva abigaragaza
 Ati: "Ahandi ho inama nshingamategeko ya Amerika canke reta ya Amerika ntiyari kuba yatunze urutoke Urwanda mu buryo butaziguye, nk’abashigikiye umugwi w’iterabwoba wa M23"
 Patrick Muyaya avuga ko kubera izo mvo Urwanda rudashobora kuba mu bihugu bizoterera ingabo zizorungikwa muri Congo n’ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Afrika y’ubuseruko, EAC,  gufasha kugwanya imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho harimwo na M23
 Abakuru b’ibihugu bemeje, mu nama yabahuje i Nairobi muri Kenya mu ntango z’iyi ndwi, ko izo ngabo zirungikwa ”buno nyene” ariko nta kirangaminsi catanzwe
 Umuvugizi wa reta ya Congo yemeza ko abakuru b’ibihugu bemeje ko muri izo ngabo ata z’Urwanda zizoba zirimwo
 Ariko itangazo ryasohowe n’ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu ca Kenya ari nawe yari arongoye iyo nama, ntaco ryavuze ku bihugu bitazoba birimwo
 Patrick Muyaya avuga ati: “Kuri twebwe, ni ibintu vyumvikana ko Urwanda rudashobora kubamwo mu bihugu bizorungika ingabo muri Congo
 Abakuru b’ibihugu bavyemeje uko
 ”Nta kuntu hoba ingabo ziza kugarukana amahoro mu gihe kandi zishigikiye umugwi dufata ko ari uw’iterabwoba”
 Patrick Muyaya avuga ko ingabo za EAC zizoba zije kugwanya imigwi yose yitwaje ibigwanisho itazoba yemeye kubishira hasi nk’uko abakuru b’ibihugu babisavye
 Major Willy Ngoma avugira M23 avuga ko izo ngabo za EAC “ata bwoba ziduteye”
 Avuga kandi ko kuba reta ya Kinshasa iwita umugwi w’iterabwoba ataco biwubwiye
 Major Ngoma avuga ko reta ya Congo "hari amasezerano twasinye nayo” i Nairobi mu 2013
 Uwo mugwi usigaye igenzura igisagara ca Bunagana uvuga ko utazokivamwo hatabaye ibiganiro na reta ya Congo kugira amasezerano bumvikanye aje mu ngiro
 Asaba ibihugu vy'akarere kwotsa igitutu reta ya Congo kugira ayo masezerano ashirwe mu ngiro

Umuhanuzi wa prezida wa Ukraine wo mu rwego rwo hejuru avuga ko intambara ibera mu bisagara vyo mu buseruko vya Severodonetsk na Lysychansk iteye "ku ndunduro"
 Oleksiy Arestovych yavuze ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zishobora ubu vuba kuzunguruka ivyo bisagara bibiri vy'amahasa, zivyonkore kuri Ukraine
 Yagize ati: "Amayeri y'Uburusiya ariko arashika ku ntsinzi, ariko ntibarabishikako
" Ivyo abivuze mu gihe prezida Volodymyr Zelensky   yagirije Uburusiya kugerageza "gusambura" akarere ka Donbas
 Muri video yasohoye mw'ijoro Volodymyr Zelensky yavuze ati:v" Hari ibitero vyinshi vy'indege na vya muzinga muri Donbas
 Intumbero y'abaduteye ntiyahindutse, bashaka, buke buke, gusambura akarere ka Donbas
" Yongeye gutera akamo abategetsi ba Buraya kunyarutsa guha ibigwanisho vya rutura  ingabo ziwe
 Yagize ati: "Turasubiye gusubiramwo  gusaba kunyarutsa kuturungika  ibigwanisho muri Ukraine
 Igikenewe n'ukunganya inguvu ku rubuga rw'intambara kugira duhagarike abo bicanyi no kubasubiza inyuma y'imbibe za Ukraine
" Mu makuru yo ku musi ku musi, ubushikiranganji bw'Ubwongereza bwo kwivuna abansi buvuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zimaze kwigira imbere ibirometero 5 uja mu bumanuko mu micungararo ya Lysychansk muri iyi ndwi
 Abategetsi ba UK bavuga bati: "Bamwe mu basirikare ba Ukraine baravuyeyo, nkeka batinya ko babazunguruka
 Kuba abarusiya bamaze gutera intambwe muri ako karere n'ukubera ukwiyongera kw'ingabo muri ako karere hamwe no kukarasa cane
" Ku musi wa gatatu, Haidai yavuze ko ibitero vy'Uburusiya "vyasambuye cane inyubakwa n'amazu" i Lysychansk
 Yongeyeko ko Severodonetsk na yo nyene iraswa "buri musi", n'aho ingabo z'Uburusiya zamaze gufata igice kinini c'ico gisagara
 Abasivile amajana n'amajana bagoswe n'iyo ntambara, mu gihe benshi bariko bararondera ubuhungiro mw'izine ya Azot
 Mu tundi turere, Uburusiya bwasubiriye kugira ibitero ku gisagara kigira kabiri ca Ukraine, Khakiv, ku musi wa gatatu mu gitondo
 Abasivile benshi bari batanguye kugaruka muri ico gisagara inyuma y'aho ingabo z'Uburusiya zisubirijwe inyuma, ariko ubu ubwoba buriko burongerekana ko Uburusiya bushobora kuba buriko burategura ibindi bitero bishasha muri ako karere
 Hagati aho, Uburusiya bwagiriza Ukraine gukoresha indege zitagira umudereva mu kugira ibitero kw'ihinguriro ry'ibitoro ryo mu karere ka Rostov, kegereye urubibe rwa Ukraine

Umugabo w’Umwongereza aherutse gucirirwa urwo gupfa na sentare ikorana n’Uburusiya kubera yariko arwanira Ukraine yabwiwe ko ategerezwa kunyongwa uko bitegekanijwe, nk’uko umuryango wiwe ubivuga
 Aiden Aslin na Shaun Pinner baciriwe urubanza rwo gupfa na sentare itemewe ku rwego mpuzamakungu yo mu citwa Repubulika ya Donetsk (Donetsk People's Republic, DPR)
 Aslin yabwiye umuryango wiwe ko abamufashe mpiri bamubwiye ko abategetsi b’Ubwongereza ata twigoro bigeze bagira two kurondera kumurekuza
 Umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza w’imigenderanire yaravuganye n’abategetsi ba Ukraine kuri iki kibazo mu ntango z’uku kwa gatandatu
 Liz Truss avuga ko we na mugenziwe wa Ukraine Dmytro Kuleba bavuganye ku twigoro two “kurekuza impfungwa z’intambara ziri mu minwe y’abakorana n’Uburusiya” akaba avuga ko izi manza z’urupfu “ziteye isoni kandi ntizemewe na gato”
 Ubushikiranganji bw’imigenderanire buzwi ko buriko burakora amatohoza ku Bongereza bafatiwe muri Ukraine, kandi ko bufata mu mugongo imiryango ya Aslin na Pinner
 Mu muryango wa Aslin bavuga ko bavuganye nawe kuri terefone akaba yababwiye ko abamufise mu minwe bamubwiye ko “umwanya uriko uramuherana”
 Inakuru wiwe Pamela Hall yabwiye BBC ati: “Nta majambo, ni ukuri nta majambo, ni umubabaro udasanzwe ku muntu uwo ari we wese ubonye nk’umunyamuryango wawe aterwa ubwoba nk’uku”
 “Aiden yari yuzuye uburakari igihe yavugana na nyina wiwe muri kino gitondo
 Ikintu nyamukuru ni uko Aiden yavuze ko DPR yamubwiye ko ata muntu n’umwe mu Bwongereza arigera avugana nabo, kandi ko agiye kunyongwa”
 “Ndemera ivyo Aiden yatubwiye, ko mu gihe abategetsi ba DPR ataco bobwirwa bazoca bamunyonga
 Nizere ko ibi atari vyo”
 Aslin na Pinner bimukiye muri Ukraine mu 2018, bamaze imyaka bari mu gisirikare ca Ukraine imbere y’igitero c’Uburusiya
 Bompi bari bafise abakunzi b’abanya-Ukraine kandi iki gihugu cari camaze kuba rwabo
 Bafashwe inyuma y’indwi zitari nke barwanira muri Mariupol yari imaze igihe kitari gito yagoswe
 Ariko iyi sentare ikorana n’Uburusiya ibita “abacangero”, ikabagiriza ko barungitswe mu ntambara yo hanze mu ntumbero yo guca amahera
 Bagirijwe ivyaha birimwo kwigarurira ubutegetsi ku nguvu, kandi ko bari mu myimenyerezo yo gukora ibitero vy’iterabwoba, nk’uko bivugwa n'itororokanizo ry'amakuru RIA Novosti rya reta y'Uburusiya
