 Lu Ke yari asanzwe aba muri Malawi igihe yashirwa ahabona na BBC Africa Eye, igisata ca BBC cegeranya amakuru y’igendereza, aho avugwa ko yakoresheje abana mu gufata amashusho y’indamukanyo yihariye, amwe muri yo arimwo ibintu bishingiye kw’ivanguraruhu
 Aya mavidewo ashobora kugurwa gushika ku madorari 70 y’abanyamerika ku mbuga hwaniro na ngurukanabumenyi zo mu Bushinwa
 Lu Ke arahakana ko ata mavidewo yo gutyoza yakoze
