Iryinyo ry’inzahabu ni co gisigarira conyene c’uwaharaniye intahe y’ukwikukira kwa Congo, Patrice Lumumba
 Inyuma yo kugandagurwa mu 1961 n’umurwi w’abasirikare wari ujejwe kunyonga ushigikiwe n’Ububirigi bwahoze butwara iki gihugu mu gihe c’ubukoloni, ikiziga ciwe cahambwe mu mva ntoya, mu nyuma kirazurwa, gitwarwa ku birometero 200, kirahambwa gushasha, congera kirazurwa hanyuma kirahimbagurwamwo, impera ya vyose bagituriza aside (acide)
 Ibi vyagiye kwemezwa n’uwari umukuru w’igipolisi w’umubirigi, Gerard Soete, ari nawe yahagarikiye isamburwa ry’ibisigarira vya Lumumba, yongera atwara iri ryinyo
 Yavuze kandi ko hari n’irindi rya kabiri n’intoke zibiri, ariko ibi ntibirashobora gutorwa
 Iri ryinyo ryitezwe gushikirizwa umuryango wiwe mu birori bizobera i Buruseri (Bruxelles) mu Bubirigi
 Iyi ngendo ya Soete yo kunyegeza ibihimba vy’umubiri yibutsa inyifato y’abategetsi ba gikoloni mu kiringo c’imyaka mirongo aho babitwara iwabo ngo bizobe icibutso
 Ariko kandi cabaye igikorwa ca nyuma c’agasuzuguro gakorewe uno mugabo yafatwa n’Ububirigi nk’umwansi
 Soete, igihe yaboneka mw’ireresi yo mu 1999, yavuze ko iryo ryinyo n’intoke yatwaye vyari “nk’ubwoko bw’igikombe c’uruhigi”
 Uru rurimi ruvuga ko ku bapolisi b’ababirigi, Lumumba – yashimagizwa ku mugabane wose nk’uwari ayoboye urugamba rwo kwikura mu buja -  atari umuntu
 Ku mukobwa wa Lumumba, Juliana, ikibazo ni ukumenya nimba abakoze ibi bari koko ibiremwamuntu
 Abaza ati: “Kugira ngo ukore ikintu nk’iki, uba ufise urwanko rungana gute?” Yabwye BBC ati: “Ibi bitwibutsa ivyakozwe n’aba-Nazi, kunyaga ibihimba vy’abantu – kandi iki ni icaha gikorerwa kiremwamuntu”
 Lumumba yagiye kuba umushikiranganji wa mbere afise imyaka 34
 Inyuma yo gutorwa mu myaka ya nyuma y’ubukoloni, yarongoye reta y’igihugu gishasha cari gihejeje kuronka intahe y’ukwikukira
 Mu kwa gatandatu 1960, igihe yashikiriza ubutegetsi, Umwami Baudouin w’Ububirigi, yashimagije ubutegetsi bw’igikoroni anavuga ko sekuru wiwe, Léopold II, ari we “yateje imbere” igihugu
 Ntiyigeze avuga ku miriyoni z’abakongomani bapfuye canke bakubaguwe mu gihe c’ubutegtsi bwiwe igihe yatwara icitwa État Indépendant du Congo /Congo Free State (Reta yigenga ya Congo) nk’icibare ciwe bwite
 Uku kwanka kwemera amabi  yakozwe muri kahise kwerekanye ingene Ububirigi bwagiye buhakana ivyo bwakoze muri iki gihugu, bugiye gutangurwa kwemera muri iki gihe
 Lumumba ntiyarya umunwa
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije ritari ku rutonde rwari rwateguwe, umushikiranganji wa mbere yaneguye ubugome n’agasuzuguro vyakorewe Abakongomani
 Muri iri jambo ryari riteye ubwoba, mbere bakaba bagenda bamuciramwo n’amashi menshi ariko aravuga,  hanyuma arangije bakamushimira cane, yasiguye “ubucakara buteye isoni badukoreye ku nguvu”
 Ababirigi baguye mu gahundwe, nk’uko bivugwa n’umwigisha wa kaminuza Ludo De Witte yasohoye igitabo mbarutso ku vyerekeye igandagurwa ryiwe
 Bwari bwo bwa mbere umwirabure w’umunyafrika yubahuka gushikiriza ijambo nk’iri imbere y’abanyabulaya
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere - De Witte avuga ko yafatwa nk’umuntu atize mu binyamakuru vy’Ububirigi - yafashwe ko amaramaje umwami n’abandi bategetsi b’Ububirigi
 Bamwe bavuga ko mu gushikiriza iri jambo yari ahejeje gutera igikumu ku rupfu rwiwe, ariko igandagurwa ryiwe mu mwaka wakurikiye ryakozwe mu buryo bwo kurwana ya ntambara y’ukwikekana (guerre froide/Cold War) n’Ububirigi bwarondera kugumana ijambo muri ico gihugu
 Abanyamerika nabo nyene baragiye mu nteguro yo kumwica kubera babona ko yari guhava yiyegereza Ubumwe bw’Abasoviyeti be n’urwanko yari afitiye abakoloni, mu gihe umutegetsi umwe w’umwongereza yanditse avuga ko kumwica yari imwe mu nzira zari zihari
 Hagari aho, bisa n’uko hariho akantu ko kwankiriza umuntu uravye ingene Lumumba yatyozwa n’ingene yahigwa
 Uku kuzimanganya n’ikiziga ciwe, hamwe no kurondera gukuraho ivyemezo, bisa n’ugushaka kurondera kwibagiza Lumumba mu mitwe y’abantu
 Nta cibutso ciwe cari kwubakwa, ibi bikaba vyari gushobora gutuma bavuga ko uyu muntu atigeze abaho
 Kumuhamba vyonyene babonye ko bitari bihagije
 Hagati aho, gushika ubu baracamwibuka
 Ni cane cane umukobwa wiwe Juliana – yafashe iya mbere mu rugamba rwo kurondera ko iri ryinyo ritahukanwa, ubu akaba ari i Buruseri kuryakira
 N’akamwenyuro, aributsa ubwana bwiwe
 Nk’uwari akiri muto mu bana bose, akongera akaba umukobwa wenyene mu muryango, avuga ko yari afitaniye imigenderanire ya hafi cane na se wiwe
 Juliana yari afise “imyaka idashika itanu” igihe se wiwe agenwa nk’umushikiranganji wa mbere
 Aribuka ingene yemerewe kujana na se wiwe mu biro, “naricara ndaba dawe ariko arakora
 Kuri jewe yari dawe”
 Ariko aremeza ko se wiwe ari “uwo igihugu, kuko yapfiriye Congo


 be n’iteka n’ivyiyumviro vyiwe vyo kurwanira agateka k’umunyafrika”
 Yemeza ko guhabwa iri ryinyo mu Bubirigi no kuritahukana muri Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo ari ikimenyetso “kuko ibisigarira vyiwe bidakwiye mu bisanzwe
 Ariko ni ngombwa ko agaruka mu gihugu ciwe aho amaraso yiwe yasesekeye”
 Iri ryinyo rizozungurutswa muri iki gihugu kinini cane imbere y’uko rihambwa ku mugwa mukuru
 Umuryango wa Lumumba waramaze imyaka myinshi utazi ivyashikiye serugo kuko ubutegetsi bwagumije agacerere ku rupfu rwiwe
 Urugendo rw'iyicwa rya Lumumba kuva abaye umushikiranganji wa mbere gushika agandagurwe rwamaze amezi adashika indwi
 Inyuma y’akanya gato igihugu kironse intahe y’ukwikukira, igihugu caciye cinjira mu ntambara n’intara ya Katanga iri mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko itunze ubutare yashaka kwiyonkora, inyuma yo gutangaza ko yikuye ku gihugu
 Mu mvururu za poritike zakurikiye, ingabo z’Ububirigi zararungitswe ku rubuga kugira ngo zikingire Ababirigi, ariko kandi baca bafasha ubutegetsi bwa Katanga bwaboneka ko bwobwo budafise urwanko kuri abo bakoloni
 Lumumba we nyene nk’umushikiranganji wa mbere yahavuye abogozwa n’umukuru w’igihugu, Joseph Kasavubu, hanyuma haciye indwi imwe gusa umukuru w’ibiro bikuru vya gisirikare ico gihe, Colonel Joseph Mobutu, aca afata ubutegetsi
 Lumumba yaciye apfungwa ic’amaso, aratoroka hanyuma asubira gufatwa muri Kigarama (12) 1960, imbere y’uko apfungirwa mu burengero bw’igihugu
 Kumushira aho hantu vyaboneka ko bishobora guteza akaguma, ariho reta y’Ububirigi yasaba ko yorungikwa muri Katanga
 Ari mu ndege mu rugendo rwamushikanye muri iyo ntara ku wa 16 Nzero (1) 1961, yarakubaguwe
 Amaze kwururutswa naho nyene yarakubiswe mu gihe abategetsi ba Katanga bariko biyumbira ico bamukoza
 Amaherezo, hahavuye hemezwa ko ashirwa mu minwe y’umurwi w’abarashi wari ujejwe kunyonga hanyuma ku wa 17 Nzero araraswa arapfa, ari kumwe na bagenwize babiri
 Iki nico gihe umukuru w’igipolisi Soete yaca aseruka
 Amaze kubona ko ibiziga vyabo abantu bashobora kubibona, haciye hafatwa ingingo yo “kubizimanganya burundu
 "Nta kimenyetso na kimwe gitegererwa kugumaho”, nk’uko bivugwa n’umwe mu babibonye yasubiwemwo na De Witte mu gitabo ciwe, The Assassination of Lumumba
  Afise imisumeno, aside (acide sulfurique), yambaye ivyomeke bipfuka mu maso (masques faciaux) afise na whisky, Soete yayoboye umurwi wo kwimura, gusambura no kuzimanganya ibisigarira vyiwe
 Cari igikorwa yagiye kuvuga mu nyuma ko rwari urugendo rwo “mu muriro udahera”
 Ariko haciye imyaka hafi 40 yose, mu 1999,  kugira ngo yemere ko yagize uruhara muri aka kabi, kandi ko gushika ubwo yari agifise iryiryo ryiwe
 Avuga ko ibindi bihimba yari afise yabitaye
 Juliana agira umubabaro ku mutima yibutse igihe yumva ko hari igihimba ca se wiwe kikiriho
 N’ikigumbagumba cinshi, ati: “Uca utahura ingene niyumvise kuri iki kintu”
 Nta wuzi ico Soete yakoresheje iri ryinyo ico gihe cose yarimaranye
 Isanamu yaryerekanye riri mu gasandugu, ariko nta wuzi nimba yari arishize kumugaragaro
 Ariko ryari rikiri mu minwe y’umuryango wiwe
 Ryasubiye kuvugwa mu 2016 igihe umukobwa wa Soete, Godelieve, atanze ikiganiro ku kinyamakuru co mu Bubirigi, Humo, casohotse imbere gato y’isabukuru igira 55 y’igandagurwa rya Lumumba
 Yagarutse ku magorwa se wiwe yagize ku mutima kubera ivyo yakoze
 Madame  Soete kandi yiyumviriye ko umuryango wiwe ukwiye gusabwa ikigongwe ku mategeko abategetsi b’Ububirigi bahaye se wiwe
 Avuga ko se wiwe yagumanye ububiko bwihariye kandi ko, n’aho inyuma y’aho apfiriye, vyinshi vyatawe, wewe yashoboye “gushingura ahadata ibintu bikomeye”
 Bimwe muri ivyo bintu ni iri ryinyo yari yazanye kugira yereke uwariko aramugirisha ikiganiro hamwe n’uwafata amasanamu
 Ryaciye rifatwa n’igipolisi c’Ububirigi inyuma y’aho De Witte yitwariye, hanyuma inyuma y’urubanza rwamaze imyaka ine, sentare yahavuye ifata ingingo y’uko risubizwa umuryango wa Lumumba
 Mu rugamba rwo kubohoza iri ryinyo, umukobwa wa Lumumba yandikiye umwami Philippe ikete ry’icese riteye agahinda
 Yabajije ati: “Kubera iki, inyuma y’iri gandagurwa ry’agahomerabunwa, ibisigarira vya Lumumba bibandanya kuba umushaha uyerera, ata n’imva yo kumushinguramwo”? Iri ryinyo ni ryamara gusubizwa, uyu yahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere azoshingurwa burundu mu ntatemwa idasanzwe ku mugwa mukuru, Kinshasa
 Georges Nzongola-Ntalaja, umuhinga muri kahise akaba ari we aserukira Congo muri ONU, avuga ati: “Ibi ni vyo dusanzwe dukora mu mico yacu, turakunda gushingura abacu bashengeye”
 “Ni ihumure ku muryango no ku banyagihugu ba Congo kuko Lumumba ni incungu yacu kandi twipfuza kumushingurana iteka”
 Ariko n’aho yoshinguranwa iteka, ni ngombwa kwibuka akahise
 Igitabo ca De Witte, kije kuzimya imyaka myinshi y’agacerere, catumye hashingwa umurwi w’amatohoza mu nama nshingamateka mu 1999, ufise igikorwa co kwiga neza “ingene iri gandagurwa ryagenze neza na neza, n’uruhara abanyaporitike b’Ububirigi boba barabigizemwo”
 Mu vyo washitseko, wanditse ko “amarangamutima ya poritike mpuzamakungu yari atandukanye” mu myaka ya 1960
 Hagati aho, n’aho uterekanye urwandiko rutegeka igandangurwa rya Lumumba, iri tohoza ryasanze harimwo bamwe mu bari muri reta “bagize uruhara mu vyatumye agandagurwa”
 Ico gihe, uwari umushikiranganji ajejwe imigenderanire, Louis Michel, yarasavye “imbabazi” yongera avuga ko ababajwe cane n’ivyashikiye umuryango wa Lumumba n’abanyagihugu ba Congo
 Prof
 Nzongola-Ntalaja, avugana na BBC ku giti ciwe, ntiyemera ko Ububirigi bwemera koko uruhara rwabwo mw’iryo gandagurwa
 Ati: “Ububirigi buranka kwemanga ivyo buzi ko bwakoze – rero ntibihagije”
 Abashikirizamanza b’ababirigi  bafata iri gandagurwa nk’icaha co mu ntambara ariko 10 kuri 12 bikekwa ko babukoze barapfuye, kandi, inyuma y’imyaka cumi, itohoza rigenda buke buke cane
 Gushikiriza iri ryinyo kizoba ari ikindi gikorwa mu nzira yo kunywanisha Ububirigi na DR Congo kuri kahise k’ubukoloni n’igandagurwa rya Lumumba
 Umukobwa wiwe ati: “Ni intambwe – dukeneye gutera tuja imbere”
 Ariko kandi, avuga ko no ku ruhande rw’abakongomani bakeneye kwikubita agashi, kuko bamwe muri bagenziwe hari abagize uruhara mu rupfu rwa se wiwe
 “Ni ngombwa ko twemera kahise kacu – kaba keza canke kabi”
 Asa n’uwuvuga ijambo afise igihagararo nk’ic’uwahoze ari umushikiranganji wa mbere, avuga ati: “Turakeneye kumenya kahise kacu, kwubaka kazoza kacu no kubaho muri kubu”
 Ihambwa ry’iri ryinyo – igikorwa gitegekanijwe kuba ku musi w’isabukuru y’imyaka 61 y’ijambo karuhariwe rya Lumumba ku musi w’ukwikukira – rizoba ari akaryo keza ku gukubitiza amaso inyuma kuri kahise

Umukuru mushaha w’igisirikare c’Ubwongereza atera akamo ko kugabisha ingabo - aho yazibwiye ko zokwitegurira guhangana n’Uburusiya ku rubuga rw’intambara
 Jenerali (Gen) Sir Patrick Sanders, inyuma yo gutangura amabanga yiwe mu ndwi iheze, yashikirije ijambo inzego zose za gisirikare n’iz’abakozi ba reta, mu butumwa yashikirije ku wa 16 Ruheshi (6), ubutumwa bwabonywe na BBC
 Igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine cerekana ko ari nkenerwa “gukingira Ubwongereza no kwitegurira kurwana tugatsinda intambara ku rubuga”, nk’uko abivuga
 Yongerako y’uko igisirikare n’incuti bategerezwa kugira “ubushobozi bwo


gutsinda Uburusiya”
 Isoko ryo mu gisata co kwivuna abansi ryabwiye umunyamakuru wa BBC ajejwe amakuru yo kwivuna abansi Jonathan Beale ko ingene yashikirije ubu butumwa – bwacishijwe ku rubuga rwa intranet rw’Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi – vyari bitangaje
 Bavuga ko ibisata vya gisirikare vyose vyitegurira kurwana, ariko biragaragara ko ibintu vyahindutse
 Muri ubwo butumwa,  Gen Sir Patrick  amenyesha ko ari we mukuru w’ibiro bikuru vya gisirikare “kuva mu 1941 afashe amabanga yo kurongora igisirikare mu gihe hari ubwoba bw’intambara yo hasi i Bulaya irimwo igihugu ca rutura”
 Yongerako ati: “Igitero c’Uburusiya kitwibutsa intumbero yacu nyamukuru – gukingira Ubwongereza kandi tukama twiteguye kurwana tugatsinda intambara ku rubuga – kandi gikomeza intumbero yo guhagarika igitero c’Uburusiyabibaye ngombwa hakoreshejwe inguvu”
 Asigura ko “isi yahindutse kuva ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2) kandi ubu ni ngombwa gushinga igisirikare gishobora kurwana kiri kumwe n’incuti zacu tugatsinda Uburusiya ku rubuga rw’intambara”
 Gen Sir Patrick kandi yihaye intego yo "kwihutisha guhimiriza no kunagura igisirikare mu ntumbero yo gukomeza OTAN/NATO be no kwaka Uburusiya akaryo ko gusubira kwigarurira akarere ako ari ko kose k’Ubulaya … turi igisekuru gitegerezwa gutegura igisirikare kugira gisubire kurwana i Bulaya”
 Igitero c’Uburusiya carahinduye integuro n’ingendo vy’igisirikare gihanganye n’ikibazo co kugabanywa kw’ibitigiri mu myaka iri imbere
 Muri Ntwarante (3) 2021, reta yatangaje umugambi wo kugabanya igitigiri c’ingabo mu Gisirikare gushika kuri 72
500 gushika mu 2025
 Uburyo buhabwa igisirikare mu Bwongereza bwariyongereye imiriyaridi 3 z’amapawundi ku mwaka kuva 2016-2017, inyuma yo kugabanywa gushika ku miriyaridi 6,6 z’amapawundi hagati ya 2010 na 2017
 Uburusiya bukoresha 4
14% vy’umwimbu wo hagti mu gihugu (PIB/GDP) mu gisirikare, mu gihe Ubwongereza bukoresha hafi 2
33%, nk’uko vyerekanwa n’ibiharuro vy’ikigo IISS Global Military Balance
 Imbere y’igitero c’Uburusiya, umushikiranganji wa mbere Boris Johnson yabwiye abashingamateka mu kwezi kwa cumi na rimwe ko yabona y’uko ikiringo c’aho ibifaru (chars/tanks) bizunguruza i Bulaya twagisize inyuma
 Abajijwe uburyo bukoreshwa mu gisirikare bafatiye ku kungene agasotoro k’Uburusiya kagenda kiyongera, umushikiranganji Johnson ico gihe yavuze ati: “Ni ngombwa ko twemera y’uko ivyiyumviro vya kera vyo kurwana intamabara zikomeye z’ibifaru  ku butaka bwa Bulaya vyaheze kandi hari ibindi bintu ngirakamaro twotegerezwa gushiramwo imitahe”
 Yavuzeko gukomeza ubushobozi bwo kurwana intamabara zo mu kirere n’ubuhinga nyabwonko  ari bwo “buryo bwo kurwana intambara muri kazoza


kandi aho niho dukeneye gushika”

Umukuru w’igihugu ca Kenya, Uhuru Kenyatta yatumyeko inama y’abakuru b’ibihugu bigize ishirahamwe rya Afrika y’Ubuseruko (EAC) kuri uno wa mbere kugira bavugane ku kibazo c’amahoro n’umutekano  muri Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo (DRC), nk’uko biri mw’itangazo rya reta
 Uhuru, ari nawe arongoye ishirahamwe EAC ku wa gatatu yasavye ko horungikwa umurwi w’ingabo za EAC guhagarika imigumuko irangwa mu buseruko bw’iki gihugu giherutse kwinjira muri iri shirahamwe
 Hagati aho, DR Congo ntishaka kwumva ko Urwanda ruri mu bagize izi ngabo, ikaba mbere yarahagaritse imigenderanire na Kigali
 Iki gihugu cagiriza Urwanda ko rufasha umuhari w’inyeshamba M23 ziherutse kwigarurira igisagara ca Bunagana kiri ku rubibe
 Urwanda Ruhakana ivyo rwagirizwa
 Mw’itangazo yasohoye, Pereziza Felix Tshisekedi yagiriza Uwanda ko rurondera kwigarurira igihugu ciwe kugira ngo rwiyimbire ubutare, mbere akaba yasavye Ubwongereza gutera igitsure Kigali kugira ngo ihagarike agasotoro kayo
 Mu ndwi nkeya ziheze, icuka kibi hagati y’ibi bihugu carunyutse, mbere haraduka n’imyiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza Urwanda i Kinshasa no mu buseruko bwa Congo
 Haciye imisi ibiri, umusirikare wa Congo yarugururiye umucanwa ku bajejwe umutekano b’Urwanda ku rubibe rwa Bukavu, akomeretsa abapolisi babiri
 Kenya niyo ihagarariye ikongera ikaba n’umuhuza mu biganiro hagati ya reta ya Congo n’imihari y’inyeshamba itandukanye
 Hagati aho, ibi biganiro ntaco birashikako

Musenyeri mukuru wa Canterbury yasavye imbabazi inyuma y’aho amatohoza yerekaniye ko ikigega c’imitahe y’Ishengero rya anglicane mu Bwongereza gifitaniye isano n’ubucakara
 Aya matohoza yakozwe asabwe n’ishami ry’iri shengero, Church Commissioners, rijejwe amatungo yaryo, yerekana ko mu kiringo c’imyaka irenga 100 iki kigega cashize amafaranga menshi cane mw’ikompanyi yari ijejwe gutwara abantu mu bucakara
 Ico kigega cari kizwi mu kinjana ca 18 kw’izina rya Queen Anne’s Bounty, cahavuye gihinduka ikigo c’imitahe ishika ku miriyaridi 10,1 z’amapawundi
 Musenyeri mukuru Justin Welby avuga ko yababaye cane kwumva ishengero arongoye rifitaniye isano n’ubucakara
 Ikigega Queen Anne's Bounty cashinzwe mu 1704 mu ntumbero yo gufasha abakozi b’Imana bari bakenye
 Itohoza ku makonte yaco mu 1739 ryerekana ko umutahe  w’amapawundi 204
000 (ubu yababa imiriyoni 443 y’amapawundi nyene) washowe mw’ikompanyi South Sea Company yagurisha abacakara b'abanye-Afrika
 South Sea Company yari ifise amasezerano yihariye yo kuvana abacakara muri Afrika ibatwara mu bihugu vyatwarwa na Espagne muri Amerika y’Ubumanuko mu kiringo c’imyaka irenga 30 kuva mu myaka ya 1710
 Yatwaye ibihumbi mirongo vy’abacakara, amatohoza akerekana ko hafi 15% yabo bapfiriye mu nzira
 Ishengero rya Anglicane mu Bwongereza ryabandanije rishora imitahe muri South Sea Company gushika mu kinjana ca 19
 Uyu musenyeri mukuru avuga ati: “Uru rudandaza rw’agahomerabunwa rwafashe abagabo, abagore n’abana baremwe mw’ishusho y’Imana rubaka agateka kabo n’ubwigenge bwabo
 “Birateye isoni kubona hari bamwe mw’Ishengero bashigikiye bikomeye bakegeranya amatungo muri uru rudandaza
 “Inzira yonyene yo gukira koko kunywanisha – ari yo Yezu Kristu/Yesu Kristo aduhamagarira gufata – ni uko duhangana n’uku kuri kubabaje hanyuma tugafata ingingo”
 Ku ruhande rumwe, Ishengero ry’Ubwongereza ririshimira uruhara ryagize mu guhagarika ubucakara, rigafatira ku ruhara umuvugabutumwa wa Anglicane, William Wilberforce, yagize
 Ku rundi ruhande, ni ngombwa ko ryemera ko ryagiye ryungukira mu bucakara
 Mu myaka iheze, Ishengero rya Anglicane mu Bwongereza riherutse gusaba imbabazi ku bakozi baryo batari bake babonetse ko bari bafise abacakara
 Ryasavye imbabazi kubera ishami ryaryo rijejwe ubutumwa, The Society for the Propagation of the Gospel (twogereranya mu kirundi tuti “Umuryango wo gukwiragiza Inkuru nziza”), ryari rifise itongo ahitwa Barbados, maze rishira ikimenyetso ku bacakara ryakoresha mu gikiriza cavuga ngo SOCIETY (twogereranya n’ijambo UMURYANGO)
 Ubu rero, ku matohoza yaryo ryo nyene, ryemeye ko mu kiringo c’imyaka mirongo ikigega caryo cashoye imitahe y’amafaranga hafi yaryo yose – hampande y’ayo ryakoresheje mu kugura amatongo – mw’ikompanyi yari ifise uruhara yiharije rwo gutwara abacakara muri Amerika y’Ubumanuko
 Mu gihe abarenga inusu y’abanywanyi b’Ishengero rya Anglicane kw’isi yose bari ku mugabane wa Afrika, iyi nkuru ishobora kutorosha ibintu
 Ishengero rya Anglican mu Bwongereza ryatanguje aya matohoza mu ntumbero yo gushira ahabona kahise karyo rikavuga ko hagiye gutumwako umurwi wo kwiga inyishu ikwiriye
 Ariko umuvugizi ntazi nimba ibi bisigura ko hagiye kuba ayandi matangazo n’amasengesho, canke nimba hashobora kubamwo n’ibiganiro ku bijanye n’indishi y’akababaro mu buryo bw’amafaranga
 Aya matohoza yerekana kandi ko iki kigega cahawe intererano z’abantu bungukiye canke bafitaniye isano n’ubu bucakara bwabaye hagati y’imigabane hamwe n’ibikorwa vy’ubutunzi bwari bushingiye ku burimyi muri uru rudandaza rw’abantu
 Uyu musenyeri mukuru yongerako ati: “Ndasabiye abo bose bakozweko n’iyi nkuru kandi nibaza ko dushobora gukorera hamwe tukihweza iyindi nzira twofata”

Dr Denis Mukwege, umuganga w’umunye-Congo yatsindiye agashimwe k’amahoro kitiriwe Nobel avuga ko  kurungika muri Congo ingabo z’akarere zivuye mu bihugu birimwo  ivyagirizwa gutera igihugu ciwe ataco bizofasha
 Ishirahamwe ry’ibihugu vya Africa y’Ubuseruko, EAC - Congo yinjiyemwo mu kwezi kwa kane  - ririko rirategura kurungika ingabo zaryo gufasha kugwanya imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho muri Congo
 EAC igizwe kandi n’Urwanda, Uburundi, Uganda, Kenya, Tanzania na Sudan y‘Epfo
 Uretse ivyo bihugu bitatu vya nyuma,  bitatu vya mbere birafitaniye isano n’ikibazo c’umutekano muke mu buseruko bwa Congo
 \nUrwanda rwo Congo irwagiriza gushigikira umugwi M23 ugwana na reta mu ntara ya Kivu
 Amashirahamwe atarondera inyungu za poritike muri Congo avuga ko Uburundi bwarungitse ingabo mu karere ka Uvira muri Sud Kivu kurwanya imigwi y’abarundi yitwaje ibigwanisho ya Red Tabara na FNL
 Ingabo za  Uganda kuva mu mpera z’umwaka ziri muri Congo kugwanya ADF, umugwi witwaje ibigwanisho uturuka muri Uganda
 Dr Mukwege avuga ko kurungika ingabo za EAC zirimwo iz’ibihugu bifise uruhara mu “guhungabanya, gukora amabi no gusahura itunga ryacu ata maragamo canke amahoro bizozana”
 Umukuru mu butavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi bwa Felix Tshisekedi, Martin Fayulu, nawe  yavuze ubwa mbere ku kibazo kiri hagati y’Urwanda na Congo
 Mu kiganiro n’abamenyeshamakuru i Kinshasa ku wa  kane mw’ijoro, Fayulu yasavye reta yiwe kwirukana uwuserukira Urwanda muri ico gihugu no guhamagaza uwugiserukira i Kigali
 Fayulu avuga ko ibaye incuro ya “gatanu” Urwanda “rutera”  Congo “kuva mu 1995-1996”
 Ariko Fayulu - n’ubu hari abakimwita 'umukuru w’igihugu yatowe' inyuma yo gutsindwa na Felix Tshisekedi mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu  yo mu  2018 - yagiriza umukuru w’igihugu kuba ari we yatumye ibihugu bibanyi vya Congo mu buseruko bija mw’ihiganirwa ry’ico gihugu
 Amwagiriza kugiranira amasezerano yo mu mpisho na bimwe muri ivyo bihugu
 Ingabo za Uganda kuva mu kwezi kwa Kigarama (kwa 12) ziri muri Congo kugwanya umugwi wa ADF ukomoka muri Uganda ariko umaze imyaka uyogoza intara za Nord Kivu na Ituri mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bwa Congo
 Inzego zijejwe umutekano za Congo n’Urwanda nazo zigeze gufatanya mu kurwanya umugwi wa FDLR

Steve Rosenberg\nUmwanditsi mukuru wa BBC mu rurimi rw'ikirusiya, Moscow Kuva igisirikare c’Uburusiya giteye Ukraine, haraciye hafi amezi ane, ibihumbi n’ibihumbi vy’abasivire baramaze kwicwa, ibisagara bitari bike navyo bicika umunyota, mu gihe imiriyoni z’abanya-Ukraine nabo bataye izabo
 Ariko ejo ku wa kane, umushikiranganji w’imigenderanire Sergei Lavrov yarandavye mu maso ambwira ko ibintu bitari uko abantu bibaza
 Ati: “Twebwe ntitwateye Ukraine”
 “Twatangaje igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare kubera ata yindi nzira twari dusigaje yo gusigurira Uburengero ko kurondera kwinjiza Ukraine muri OTAN/NATO cari icaha”
 Kuva Uburusiya buteye Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), umushikiranganji Lavrov ni gake yari amaze guha ikiganiro ibinyamakuru vyo mu bihugu vy’Uburengero
 Asubiramwo amajambo avugwa na Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya) ko muri Ukraine harimwo aba-Nazi
 Abategetsi b’Uburusiya bakunze kuvuga ko igisirikare cabo kiriko “kirakura ivyiyumviro vy’iki-Nazi” mu gihugu
 Lavrov aherutse guteza uburakari igihe agerageza gusigura amajambo yafashwe nk’ibitutsi ku mukuru w’igihugu ca Ukraine, nawe akaba ari Umuyahudi, mu kuvuga mu buryo bw’agasuzuguro ko Adolf Hitler yari afise “amaraso y’Abayahudi”
 Namusubiriyemwo icegeranyo c’ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU ku bijanye n’ikigwati ca Yahidne mu ntara ya Chernihiv muri Ukraine, kivuga ko “abantu 360, harimwo abana 74 na batanu bafise ubumuga, bahatiwe n’ingabo z’Uburusiya kumara imisi 28 yose bari mu vyumba vyo mu kuzimu kw’ishure rimwe 



 Nta tuzu twa surwumwe twarimwo, nta n’amazi


abatama 10 muri bo barapfuye”
 Nca ndamubaza nti: “None uko ni kwo kurwanya Abanazi”? Yishuye ati: “Birababaje cane, ariko abaserukira ibihugu n’amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu, harimwo umukuru w’ishami rya ONU rijejwe agateka ka zina muntu, Umunyamabanga mukuru wa ONU n’abandi baserukira ONU, bariko baraterwa igitsure n’Uburengero”
 “Uburusiya ntibwera de
 Uburusiya buri ico buri
 Kandi ntitumaramazwa no kwerekana ico turi”
 Lavrov w’imyaka 72, amaze imyaka 18 aserukira Uburusiya ku rwego mpuzamakungu, ariko we n’umukobwa wiwe barafatiwe ibihano n’ibihugu vyo mu Burengero
 Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zimwagiriza ko abandanya ashikiriza amajambo y’ibinyoma mu kuvuga ko Ukraine ari yo ibasotora, kandi ko ari we abazwa igitero c’Uburusiya nk’umwe mu bagize Inama Nkuru y’igihugu ijejwe umutekano
 Niho rero nahava ndamubaza ibijanye n’imigenderanire y’Uburusiya n’Ubwongereza
 Iki gihugu kiri ku rutonde rw’ibihugu vy’abansi b’Uburusiya, nca mvuga ko kuvuga y’uko imigenderanire ari mibi kwoba ari ukworosha ibintu
 Lavrov yishuye ati: “Sinibaza ko hoba hari iyindi nzira yoba isigaye kuko yaba [Umushikiranganji wa mbere Boris] Johnson canke [Liz] Truss, bompi bavuga amenya ngo ni ngombwa ko dukubita hasi Uburusiya, ni ngombwa ko dukora ibishoboka vyose Uburusiya bugapfukama
 Bandanye, bikore rero!”
 Hari mu kwezi guheze igihe umushikiranganji w’Ubwongereza ajejwe imigenderanire yavuga ko umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yariko yiteza urubwa we nyene ku rubuga mpuzamakungu, kandi ko “dutegerezwa gukora ibishoboka vyose kugira atsindwe muri Ukraine”
 Mbajije Lavrov ingene abona Ubwongereza ubu, yavuze ko “bwasubiriye guta inyungu z’abanyagihugu mu kaga ku nyungu z’abanyaporitike”
 Narongeye ndamubaza ivyerekeye Abongereza babiri baherutse gucirirwa urubanza rwo gupfa n’abategetsi b’akarere gashaka kwiyonkora bashigikiwe n’Uburusiya mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 Ndamubwiye ko mu maso y’ibihugu vy’Uburengero Uburusiya ari bwo bubazwa ibizobabako vyose, yishuye ati: “Jewe amaso y’ibihugu vy’Uburengero nta na kimwe ambwiye
 Jewe ndajwe ishinga n’amategeko mpuzamakungu
 Nk’uko amategeko mpuzamakungu abivuga, abacangero ntibafatwa nk’abarwanyi”
 Nishuye ko aba bagabo bari basanzwe mu gisirikare ca Ukraine kandi ko batari abacangero, hanyuma Lavrov aca avuga ko ivyo bitegerezwa kwihwezwa na sentare
 Yahavuye yagiriza BBC ko idashira ahabona ukuri ku vyamye bishikira abasivire bo mu turere turi mu minwe y’abarwanyi dushaka kwiyonkora mu buseruko bwa Ukraine, “aho abasivire bari bamaze imyaka umunani baterwa amabombe n’ingabo za Kyiv”
 Nashimangiye ko mu myaka itandatu yose iheze, BBC yavuganye incuro nyinshi n’abategetsi bo mu turere dushaka kwiyonkora isaba uruhusha rwo kwinjira kugira ngo yibonere ivyariko biraba
 Igihe cose twabigerageje baratwimye uruhusha
 Uburusiya bwagiriza Ukraine ihonyabwoko
 Ariko mu 2021, abasivire umunani barishwe mu turere turi mu minwe y’inyeshamba, nk’uko bivugwa n’abategetsi b’ubutere twegamiye Uburusiya dutangaza ko twigenga, hamwe rero n’abandi indwi mu mwaka w’imbere y’aho
 Navuze ko mu gihe ubwicanyi ubwo ari bwo bwose ari akaga, ubu bwobwo ntibwabaye ihonyabwoko
 Navuze nti nimba koko harabaye ihonyabwoko, abategetsi b’uturere dushaka kwiyonkora twa Luhansk na Donetsk bari kwumva ko bikenewe ko baduha uruhusha tukinjira
 Namubajije nti “kubera iki batwankiye?”
 Yishuye ati: “Ntavyo nzi”

Igisirikare c’Urwanda, RDF, cemeje ko hari umusirikare wa Congo yarashwe arapfa inyuma yo kwinjira akarasa kandi agakomeretsa abantu muri Rubavu ku mupaka ivyo bihugu bihana
 Itangazo rya RDF rivuga ko uwo musirikare wa Congo atamenyekanye umwidondoro  yari afise inkoho yo mu bwoko bwa AK47 [Kalashinikov]
 Rivuga ko “Muri iki gitondo hafi y’isaha 08:45 [isaha zibiri n’iminota 45 zo mu gitondo], umusirikare w’umunye-Congo atamenyekanye yari yitwaje inkoho yo mu bwoko bwa AK47 yajabutse “Petite Barriere” ku rubibe rwa Rubavu atangura kurasa abajejwe umutekano b’Urwanda n’abanyagihugu basanzwe bariko barajabuka”
 Rivuga ko  yakomerekeje abapolisi babiri b’Urwanda imbere y’uko mugenzi wabo nawe amurasa akamwica
 Itangazo  rivuga ko uwo musirikare  wa Congo yiciwe ku metero 25 imbere ku butaka bw’Urwanda
 Umugwi w’abahinga ba gisirikare bo mu karere basanzwe bagenzura bakanatohoza ibibazo vy’umutekano bariko baragendera akarere ka Petite Barriere
 Icuka  cifashe nabi hagati y’Urwanda na Congo yagiriza ico gihugu gufasha umugwi witwaje ibigwanisho wa M23 mu ntambara urimwo n’ingabo za Congo mu ntara ya Nord Kivu
 Ku ruhande rwa Congo rw’umupaka ihana n’Urwanda hakurya y’aho uwo  umusirikare yiciwe, muri iyi ndwi habaye imyiyerekano y’abanye-Congo yo kwiyama Urwanda
 Urwanda rurahakana ivyo ruregwa na Congo
 Ku wa gatatu  urwego rukuru rujejwe umutekano muri Congo rwasavye reta y’ico gihugu guhagarika amasezerano yose rufitaniye n’Urwanda kubera "igitero rwagavye" kuri Congo
 Itangazo ry’inama  yarwo idasanzwe yari irongowe n’umukuru w’igihugu Felix Tshisekedi, yasavye reta arongoye “gutegeka Urwanda gukura ako kanya ingabo zarwo zinyegeza  inyuma y’umutwe w’iterabwoba wa M23 ku butaka bwa Congo"
 Icegera c’umuvugizi wa reta y’Urwanda, Alain Mukuralinda, yavuze ati "reka dutegereze turebe" niba icyemezo cy'iyo nama reta izacemeza

