Inyuma y’indwi nkeya umukuru wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika agabishije Ubushinwa kuri Taiwan, Pékin iriyamiriza bikomeye aya majambo, ivuga ko izorwanya n’inguvu zayo zose iciyumviro ico ari co cose c’ukwikukira kwa Taiwan
 Ku wa Mungu, umushikiranganji w’Ubushinwa ajejwe kwivuna abansi Jenerali Wei Fenghe yaragirije cane cane Amerika ko ishigikiye ukwikukira kw’iri zinga, avuga ko iriko “irahonyanga ivyo yiyemeje kuri Taiwan” no “kwivanga” mu bibazo vy’Ubushinwa
 Ari mw’ikoraniro Shangri-la Dialogue, ikoraniro ryiga ku bijanye n’umutekano wa Aziya ririko ribera muri Singapour, yavuze ati: “Reka ntomore iki kintu neza: mu gihe hogira umuntu uwo ari we wese yohirahira gutandukanya Taiwan akayikura ku Busshinwa, ntituzohingitanya kurwana
 "Tuzorwana n’inguvu zacu zose gushika ku wa nyuma
 Aya niyo mahirwe yonyene y’Ubushinwa”
 Avuze aya majambo inyuma y’ubutumwa Perezida Joe Biden aherutse guha Ubushinwa ko buriko “bufyina ahafyikiye” mu kugururira indege zabwo hafi ya Taiwan
 Yiyemeje ko azokingira iri zinga mu gihe ryoramuka ritewe
 Taiwan, izinga ryifata nk’igihugu cigenga, yamye irwanirwa n’Ubushinwa
 Ariko Taiwan kandi igendera kuri Amerika nk’incuti yayo ya hafi gusumba, mu gihe Washington ifise itegeko riyisaba gufasha iri zinga kwivuna umwansi
 Ivyo guterana amajambo vyagiye kwunyuka igihe Ubushinwa burungitse indege z’intambara mu kirere ca Taiwan – mu gasotoro kanini cane muri uno mwaka, aha hakaba hari mu kwezi guheze – mu gihe Amerika nayo yarungitse amato y’intambara mu mazi ya Taiwan
 None ubwo Amerika n’Ubushinwa vyoba biriko bitera bija mu mishamirano ya gisirikare? Hari ubwoba bwinshi ko hashobora kwaduka intambara mu gihe Ubushinwa bwotera Taiwan
 Pékin yarigeze kuvuga ko izokwisubiza iri zinga hakoreshejwe inguvu bibaye ngombwa
 Ariko abihweza ibintu n’ibindi babona ko ibi bidashoboka  - muri iki gihe
 Hari impari nimba Ubushinwa koko bufise inguvu za gisirikare zihagije kugira ngo ikore igitero, mu gihe Taiwan ibandanya yegeranya inguvu zo mu kirere no mu mazi
 Ariko abenshi baremera ko Pékin izi neza ko yohahombera cane kandi ko vyotera akaga – atari ku Bushinwa gusa, ariko no kw’isi yose
 "Hari vyinshi bivugwa, ariko Abashinwa bategerezwa kuhagabira cane nu gihe boba bategura gutera Taiwan, cane cane ko ari ikibazo cegeranye n’ica Ukraine
 Ubutunzi bw’Ubushinwa burafitaniye isano rinini cane n’ubutunzi bw’isi gusumba uko ubwo Uburusiya bumeze”, ibi bikaba bivugwa na William Choong wo mu kigo gikurikirana ibibazo vyo mu karere ka Aziya y’ubumanuko bushira ubuseruko (Institute of Southeast Asian Studies)
 Ubushinwa bubandanya busaba ko “busubirana na Taiwan mu mahoro” – ico Jenerali Wei yashimitseko ku wa Mungu – kandi ko buzofata ingingo mu gihe gusa bwosotorwa
 Rero icotuma umuriro waka ni uko Taiwan itangaza ku mugaragaro ko yikukiye
 Ariko iki nico Perezida Tsai Ing-wen azibira, n’aho yama avuga ko ari igihugu cigenga
 Abanya - Taiwan hafi bose barashigikiye iki ciyumviro, ko ibintu vyoguma uko biri, n’aho hari inkehwa bavuga ko bashaka gushika ku bwigenge
 Ariko kandi, ni nk’uko Amerika idashaka kwinjizwa mu ntambara yotuma ikoresha uburyo bwinshi bwa gisirikare muri Aziya, kandi ibandanya ivuga ko itipfuza intambara
 Umunyamabanga wa reta ajejwe kwivuna abansi, Lloyd Austin nawe nyene akaba yaritavye iri koraniro, mw’ijanbo yashikirije yavuze ko Amerika idashigikiye ukwikukira kwa Taiwan, kandi ko idakeney “intambara nshasha y’ukwikekana [Guerre froide/Cold War])
 Collin Koh, umushakashatsi kw’ishure S Rajaratnam School of International Studies  avuga ati: "Impande zompi ntizirota zidegura ku kibazo ca Taiwan
 "Ariko bategerezwa kuraba neza, na rirya batagomba kuboneka ko ari bo batuma ibintu bisubira inyuma”
 “Ariko aho nyene kandi, barazi neza  ko bitokworoha mu gihe boja mu ntambara yeruye
 "Bariko barabana ku jisho ivyo umwe wese avuga, kandi buri ruhande ruriko rugerageza kworosha ibintu”
 Kubona Jen Wei na Austin babonana ukwabo mw’ikoraniro Shangri-la Dialogue cabaye ikintu ciza, kuko bisigura ko impande zompi zishaka kwerekana ko “bagishaka kwicara bakabiganirako, bagashika mu masezerano, bakemera ko hari ivyo badategerezwa kubona kumwe”
 Koh avuga ko ibi bishobora gutuma haba ibiganiro hagati y’ibi bisirikare bibiri vyotuma icuka kibi coteza intambara kivaho, hanyuma hagasubira kunagurwa “ingendo y’ibiganiro” yari ibuze mu gihe c’ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump
 Ariko n’aho biri uko, uku guterana amajambo hagati y’Ubushinwa na Amerika kwitezwe kuzobandanya uku
 Ubushinwa bufise mbere no kwongereza “ibikorwa vy’agasotoro” mu ntumbero yo gutesha umutwe ingabo za Taiwan  - nko kurungika izindi ndege z’intambara  - canke mu gukwiragiza ibinyoma, nk’uko bivugwa na Dr
 Ian Chong, umuhinga w’umushinwa kuri kaminuza ya Singapour
 Taiwan yarigeze kwagiriza Ubushinwa ko bwateguye isekeza yo gukwiragiza ibinyoma muri ino misi iri zinga ryegereje amatora, bikaba vyitezwe ko iri zinga ritegura amatora akomeye mu mpera z’uno mwaka
 Kuri Amerika n’Ubushinwa n’ibura, “nta shaka ririho ryo guhindura aho bihagaze” ubu, na rirya cane cane himirije ibikorwa bikomye – amatora yo muri Munyonyo (11) muri Amerika, hamwe n’ikoraniro rigira 20 ry’umugambwe w’aba Komunista  mu Bushinwa mu gice ca kabiri c’uno mwaka aho Perezida Xi Jinping yiteze gutsimbataza ubutegetsi bwiwe
 Dr Chong ati: “Iciza kihari ni uko ata ruhande na rumwe rushaka ko ibintu vyunyuka”
 “Ariko n’aho ibintu bitokwunyuka ntibisigura ko tuzoba duhagaze neza
 Rero twese turacari muri iki kibazo mu gihe kanaka”

Bamwe mu bashika kurondera ubuhungiro muri UK bazorungikwa mu Rwanda kugira ivyabo vyo gusaba ubuhungiro vyigwe n’ico gihugu
 Uwo mugambi ugiye kugeragezwa ku kiringo c’imyaka itanu uzorungika bamwe mu mpunzi mu Rwanda, kugira baje gusaba ubuhungiro muri ico gihugu
 Aba mbere bitezwe kurungikwa kuri uyu wa kabiri itariki 14 ukwezi kwa Ruheshi (kwa 6)
 Uwo mugambi werekeye cane cane abimukira bakiri bato kandi bakiri bonyene (celibataires) bashika baciye mu buryo reta ivuga ko  ‘’bunyuranye n’amategeko, bubangamye canke budakenewe,” nko mu bwato canke mu kwinyegeza mu ma kamyo
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere w’Ubwongereza Boris Jonhson yavuze ko Urwanda arirwo ruzokwitaho abarungitsweyo, rubahe amahirwe angana mu kuronka ubuzi  n’ibindi vya nkenerwa
 Uwari we wese yinjiye mu Bwongereza inyuma y’itariki ya 1 Nzero (ukwezi kwa mbere) ashobora kurungikwa, ataho kugarukiriza ku gitigiri, nk’uko umushikiranganji wa mbere yavuze
 Ubwa mbere abantu 37 ni bo bari kurungikwa ku wa kabiri, ariko ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati mu gihugu bwabwiye BBC ko intambamyi zifatiye ku mategeko zagabanuye cane ico gitigiri
 Ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati buvuga ko abantu umunani aribo baja kurungikwa muri iyo ndege, ariko ishirahamwe ry’abagiraneza Care4Calais rivuga ko abo bantu ari indwi gusa
 Umunyamabanga wa reta ajejwe imigenderanire Liz Truss yashimangiye ko indege yo ku wa kabiri ija guhaguruka, n’aho yoba itwaye abantu bari ku rushi
 Yongeyeko ati: ‘’N’ubwo boba batari ku ndege y’uyu munsi, bazogenda mu ndege zikurikira zizoja mu Rwanda
” Amashirahamwe y’abagiraneza n’abashingwamanza bahagarariye  abarondera ubuhungiro batanguje urugamba rushingiye ku mategeko rwo kurwanya uwo mugambi , bavuga ko bafise amakenga ku gateka ka zina muntu
 Ku wa mbere sentare isubiramwo imanza  yanse kubuza indege kujana mu Rwanda aba mbere mu basaba ubuhungiro ku rubanza rwari rwashingishijwe na  sendika Public and Commercial Services Union hamwe n’amashirahamwe y’abagiraneza Care4Calais na Detention Action
 Hari n’izindi ntambamyi zishingiye ku mategeko nazo zija kwumvirizwa muri sentare imbere y’uko indege ihagaruka
 Asylum Aid ivuga ko ukurungika abarondera ubuhungiro ari akarenganyo kuko ata mwanya ukwiye uhari kugirango baronke ubwunganizi mu mategeko kandi bunguruze urubanza rw’uburenganzira bwo kuguma mu Bwongereza
 Ayandi mashirahamwe aharanira agateka ka zina muntu afise amakenga niba Urwanda koko ari igihugu gitekanye co kurungikamwo abo bantu, akagabisha ko uwo mugambi uteye kubiri n’amasezerano y’ishirahamwe rya Buraya yerekeye agateka ka zina muntu
 Umushikirangani wa mbere yavuze ko reta yari yabonye hakiri kare ko hazoba ‘’abashingwamanza bakerebutse” bazobera intambamyi uwo mugambi
 Yagirije abaharanira uburenganzira kurondera ko  “ikibazo c’abimukira  kirabwa imiryango yuguruye”, avuga ko   bikenewe cane ko ”hahagarikwa ibikorwa vy’imigwi vy’inkozi z’ikibi” vyo kujabutsa abantu mu kinyegero
 Amakuru avuga ko Urwanda rwasubiyemwo amazu y’uburaro hafi y’umurwa mukuru Kigali kugura azokwakire abo bimukira barungikwa bavuye mu Bwongereza
 Ico gihugu gisanzwe gihaye indaro impunzi 150
000 ziva mu  bihugu bibanyi vy’Uburundi  na Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo
 Rusanzwe ruhaye indaro kandi abimukira bagerageje kujabuka Mediterranee baja i Buraya baciye muri Libya
 Bamwe bakora nk’abarimyi, abandi nk’abakozi bo mu ngo
 Benshi nta kazi bafise, babeshejweho n’imfashanyo ya reta y’ama pound 35 (arenga ibihumbi 40 vy’amafaranga y’Urwanda) ku kwezi
 Reta y’Urwanda ivuga ko igihugu cakoze ‘’igitangaro’’ c’iterambere kuva mu 1994, igihe jenoside yahitana abantu barenga 800
000
 Amafaranga umunyagihugu yinjiza ku mwaka yariyongeye cane kuva ico gihe
 Imyaka yo  kuramba  yiyongeye incuro icumi kuva mu 1990 ishika ku 69
 Ariko abashika 70 kw’ijana ku  banyagihugu miriyoni 13, babeshejweho n’ukurima, bisigura ko barya, badashora ivyo bimbura
 Reta ivuga ko ugusaba ubuhungiro mu Bwongereza ubu bitwara miriyaridi 1,5 z’ama pound ku mwaka, ayarenga miriyoni 4,7 z’ama pound akaba akoreshwa buri munsi mu kuriha amahoteri abimukira batagira uburaro  bashirwamwo
 Kubakura mu Bwongereza n’indege zakoteshejwe vyatwa ama ama pound arenga 13
000 ku muntu mu 2020
 Umushikiranganji w’intwaro yo hagati Tom Pursglove yavuze ko amafaranga angana miriyoni 120 z’ama pound y’ibanze azoheza agakurikirwa n’ayandi azohabwa Urwanda mu gihe ruzoba rubandanya kwakira abandi
 Ubwongereza bugiye gushira kandi miriyoni 120 z’ama pound mw’iterambere n’izamuka ry’ubutunzi vy’Urwanda
 Yavuze ko amafaranga azosohoka “asa n’ayangana n’ayo dusanzwe dusohora muri iki gihe ku basaba ubuhungiro”, kandi ko “ku gihe kirekire, mu kugabanya umuzo, ivyo bizodufasha kubika amafaranga”
 Ariko, uwukurikirana ibibazo vyo mu ntwaro hagati mu mugambwe utavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi Yvette Cooper yavuze ko “amafaranga yose azokoreshwa azoba menshi kurusha”
 Habaye igereranywa n’amafaranga Austrialia isohora kugira ama dosiye y’abarondera ubuhungiro muri ico gihugu yigirwe hanze, ayo nayo akaba yangana na miriyoni 546 z’ama pound mu 2021-22
 Liz Truss  yanse kuvuga amafaranga indege yo ku wa kabiri izotwara, ahubwo avuga ko ikiguzi ku gucuruza abantu no kurondera ubuhungiro mu buryo butemewe n’amategeko bitwara amafaranga  “menshi cane” umutangakori
 Uwo mugambi wo mu Rwanda wamenyeshejwe ubwa mbere na reta y’Ubwongereza itariki 14 Ndamukiza (ukwezi kwa kane)
 Hagati y’itariki 18 Ndamukiza na 5 Ruheshi (ukwa gatandatu), abarondera ubuhungiro bashika 3
599 nibo bizwi ko bajabutse mu bwato buto buto, hakurikijwe ibitigiri bitangwa n’ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi
 N’ubwo abo bantu ari bake ugereranije na 4
554 binjiye hagati ya Ndamukiza na Ruheshi 2021, igitigiri gishobora kwiyongera  niyo haboneka  ibiharuro vyose vy’ikiringo co hagati ya Ndamukiza na Ruheshi
 Mu mwaka wose wa 2021, abantu 28
526 bazwi ko bajabutse mu bwato buto buto – bavuye ku 8
404 mu 2020
 Igitigiri cose c’uyu mwaka citezwe ko kizoba kiri hejuru cane kuruta mu mwaka uheze, nk’uko bivugwa  n’abarongoye sendika Border Force
 Mu 2021, 75 kw’ijana y’abaje bari abagabo bari hagati y’imyaka 18 na 39
 Abashika 5 kw’ijana bari abagabo bafise imyaka irenga 40, 7 kw’ijana bari abagore bafise imyaka irenga 18, abana bafise munsi y’imyaka 18 bangana na 12 kw’ijana (muri abo batatu kuri bane bakaba bari abahungu)
 Imbere y’aho abanya-Iran nibo bari benshi mu baza - 80 kw’ijana mu 2018, na 66 kw’ijana mu 2019
 Ubu vuba abantu barushirijeho kuba uruvange rw’ibihugu barurukamwo
 Abanya-Iran bashika 30 kw’ijana y’abaza mu bwato buto buto mu mwaka uheze, mu gihe 21 kw’ijana bari abanya-Iraq, 11 kw’ijana abanya-Eritrea na 9 kw’ijana b’abanya-Syria hakuwrikijwe ibiharuro bitangwa n’ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati

Ibiraro vyose vyinjira mu gisagara ca Severodonetsk muri Ukraine vyarabomowe, nk’uko bivugwa na buramatari
 Mu gihe iki gisagara ubu cazibiwe burundu, Serhiy Haidai avuga ko ivyo gufasha no guhungisha abasivire ubu ari ibinti bitagishoboka
 Intambara zikomeye ziriko zibera muri ico gisagara aho abategetsi ba Ukraine bavuga ko amabombe y’Uburusiya yomoye ingabo za Ukraine hagati muri ico gisagara
 Haraciye indwi zitari nke igisirikare c’Uburusiya kigerageza gufata Severodonetsk
 Kwigarurira Severodonetsk hamwe n’ikindi gisagara vyegeranye ca Lysychansk bishobora gutuma Uburusiya bugenzura intara yose ya Luhansk, mu gihe ubu igice kinini cayo kiri mu minwe y’inyeshamba zishaka kwiyonkora kuri Ukraine zishigikiwe n’Uburusiya
 Haidai yanditse ku rubuga rwa Instagram ko ibiraro vyose vyinjira muri Severodonetsk vyabomowe
 Yongerako y’uko abanyagihugu basigaye  muri iki gisagara babayeho mu “buzima bubi cane”
 Jordan Gatley yahoze ari mu ngabo z‘Ubwongereza ni umwe mu bahasize ubuzima bariko bagerageza kurwanira iki gisagara, nk’uko umuryango wiwe wavyemeje ku wa Mungu
 Umukuru w’igihugu ca Ukraine, Volodomyr Zelensky, avuga ko igiciro c’abantu bamaze kuhasiga ubuzima barwanira Severodonetsk “giteye ubwoba”
 Avuga ko ingabo za Ukraine zatanye mu mitwe n’iz’Uburusiya “hafi imetero ku yindi”
 Amakuru avuga ko ibice hafi 70% ubu biri mu minwe y’Uburusiya
 Ingabo za Ukraine zikiri mu gisagara zitegerezwa “kwishikana canke gupfa”, nk’uko bivugwa n’intumwa ya gisirikare yo mu ntara ya Donetsk iherutse gutangaza ko yikukiye ikitwa Donetsk People's Republic ishigikiwe n’Uburusiya
 Avugana n’abanyamakuru i Donesk, Eduard Basurin yavuze ati: “Ingabo za Ukraine ziri hariya [ i in Severodonetsk] ziriyo ubutakivayo
 Umutegetsi mukuru w’Uburusiya avuga ko intumbero ya Moscou yari iyo gukingira Donetsk na Luhansk ziherutse gutangaza ko ari repubulika zigenga
 Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yasubiwemwo n’itororokanirizo ry’amakuru RIA Novosti avuga ati: “Muri rusangi, gukingira izi repubulika niyo ntumbero nyamukuru y’igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare”
 Igihe Perezida Vladimir Putin atanguza intambara ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), yavuga ko intumbero y’Uburusiya yari iyo “gusambura igisirikare no gukuraho ivyiyumviro vy’iki-Nazi muri Ukraine”
 Mu nyuma hiyongeyeko iyindi ntumbero: gukora ibishoboka vyose kugira ngo Ukraine ntigire uruhande na rumwe yegamira
 Ejo ku wa mbere, abategetsi ba Ukraine bongeye kuvuga ko ibirwanisho bitangwa n’Uburengero bitariko birashika ningoga nk’uko vyategerezwa
 Umuhanuzi mukuru wa Perezida Zelensky yavuze ko kugira ngo bashobore guhagarika intambara ari uko igisirikare ca Ukraine “kironswa ibirwanisho bikomeye”, anashira ahabona urutonde rw’ibirwansiho rutura Kyiv ikeneye
 Avuga mu kiganiro ca BBC, Newshour, umuhanuzi wo mu bushikiranganji bwa Ukraine bujejwe kwivuna abansi yavuze ko ingabo zirwanira Severodonetsk zari kuba zarihagazeko iyo zironswa ibirwanisho bikomeye imbere y’igihe
 Yury Sak yavuze ko ingabo ziriko zirwanira iki gisagara “zikoresheje uburyo bushoboka zifise” ariko ko zishobora kuba zaravyifashemwo “neza gusumba mu kwirukana umwansi no kubohoza ubutaka bwa Ukraine iyo turonswa ibindi birwanisho bikomeye gushika ubu”
 Yongerako y’uko inguvu z’Uburusiya ziteye ubwoba – aho ingabo zabwo zitera ibisasu 50
000 ku musi, zikubaka “uruhome rwa vya muzinga, ibitero vy’indege, hamwe n’ibisasu vya misire” kuri Ukraine
 Mu ndwi nke ziheze, ibihugu vy’Uburengero vyariyemeje kurungikira Kyiv ibirwanisho birasa kure, harimwo n’Ubwongereza bwatangaje ku ncuro ya mbere ko bwari kurungika ibikoho birasa ica rimwe bibisasu vya roketi vyinshi mu ntumbero yo gufasha Ukraine kwivuna

Abacamanza bo muri sentare isubiramwo imanza mu Bwongereza banse  guhagarika indege reta y'Ubwongereza izorungika mu Rwanda ijanye aba mbere mu barondera ubuhungiro binjiye muri ico gihugu  bidaciye mu nzira zemewe n'amategeko
 Iyo ndege itegekanijwe guhaguruka ku musi w'ejo wa kabiri aho bukera
 Iyo ngingo ikurikiye iyari yafashwe na sentare nkuru ko biri mu nyungu "z'abanyagihugu" ko reta ikomeza imigambi yayo
 Muri uwo mugambi, bamwe mu binjira mu Bwongereza bidaciye mu nzira zemewe n'amategeko bazojanwa mu Rwanda babandanye gusaba ubuhungiro ariyo bari
 Abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bariko baragerageza kubuza ko abo bantu barungikwa mu Rwanda imbere y'uko  uwo mugambi usuzumwa neza ko uhuye n'amategeko mu kwezi kuza
 Iyo sentare imbere y'aho yari yabwiwe ko abantu 11 ari bo bitezwe kurungikwa mu Rwanda muri iyo ndege yo ku wa kabiri
 Ariko ishirahamwe ry'abagiraneza, Care4Calais, ryari muri abo bunguruje urubanza rwari rwaciwe na sentare nkuru, ryavuze ko abazogenda muri iyo ndege ubu ari umunani gusa
 Urubanza rwagiye muri sentare isubiramwo imanza inyuma y’aho abarushingishije barushirijwe ku wa gatanu uheze, umucanaza wa sentare nkuru agafata ingingo yo kwemerera indege ya mbere guharuruka kuri uyu wa kabiri
 Muri uwu mugambi, bamwe mu binjira mu Bwogereza badakurikije amategeko bazokwungururirzwa mu Rwanda kugira ngo basabireyo ubuhungiro
 Hazoba umwihwezo wimbitse aho sentare nkuru y’igihugu izokwumviriza ibishikirizwa n’abarwanya uwu mugambi muri rusangi imbere y’impera za Mukakaro (7)
 Mu ngingo yiwe, umucamanza Swift  wo muri sentare nkuru  yemeye ko harimwo “inyungu z’abanyagihugu” mu gihe umushikiranganji w’intwaro yo hagati Priti Patel  yoshobora gushira mu ngiro uwu mugambi
 Uwo mugambi waraneguwe cane n'amashirahamwe aharanira uburenganzira bwa zina muntu
 Reta y’Ubwongereza yo yemeza ko ugamije guca intege abafata ingendo zibangamye cane zo kwinjira mu Bwongereza
 Yaramara no kuri uyu wa mungu, hashitse 111 baje mu bwato butatu buto buto, abamaze gushika mu bwongereza  muri uyu mwaka bakaba barenga ibihumbi 10

Bisanzwe bizwi ko Vladimir Putin akunda cane Pierre le Grand/Peter the Great, ariko ubu nawe asa n’uwibona ko na we ari nka we
 Yigereranije ku mugaragaro n’uyu mu Tsar w’Umurusiya, aho agereranya igitero kuri Ukraine n’intambara za Pierre le Grand zo kwiyagurira uturere, haraciye ibinjana vyababa bitatu, akaba yaboneyeho n’akaryo ko kwerekana n’inguvu nyinshi ko intambara yiwe ari ukwigarurira ubutaka
 Intumbero za Putin zisa no kwubaka ingoma (Empire) zateje umutima uhagaze Ukraine zongera ziteza uburakari ibihugu bibanyi, harimwo na Estonia ivuga ko amajambo yiwe “adashobora kwihanganirwa na gato”
 Umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya yavuze aya majambo igihe yariko abonana n’urwaruka rw’abahinga n’aba “entrepreneurs”
 Imbere y’uko aja ku bijanye n’ubuhinga, yabanje kuvuga ivyerekeye poritike n’ubutegetsi: intambara nshasha afata ko ari ukwiha ikibanza mu makungu
 Hano abwira abamwumviriza ko Pierre le Grand/Peter the Great ari icitegererezo
 "Kumbure wohava wibaza ko yarwana na Suwede ngo yigarurire ubutaka bwabo”, niko Putin avuga, afatiye ku ntambara zo mu Buraruko (Guerres du nord/Northern Wars) zatangujwe na Pierre mu ntango z’ikinjana ca 18 igihe yariko yubaka ingoma nshasha y’Uburusiya
 "Ariko nta kintu na kimwe yigaruriye; yarisubije”! niko avuga, asigura ko aba Slaves bari babaye muri ako karere imyaka ibinjana
 "Na twebwe rero ibintu bisa n’uko, kwisubira no kwiyubaka”, niko asozera avuga, n’akamwenyuro nyene kerekana ata nkeka ko yariko avuga kuri Ukraine n’intumbero yiwe muri iki gihugu
 Abona ko ukwiyagurira Uburusiya kwatumye ubutegetsi bwa Pierre bukomera
 Putin yafashe ingendo yo gufatira kuri kahise k’Uburusiya muri kino gihe, ariko buri gihe akabikorana ubwenge bwinshi kugira ngo bijane n’intumbero yiwe muri kino gihe
 Amezi atari make imbere y’uko atera Ukraine, yasohoye urwandiko rukomeye ayo yiyamiriza uburenganzira bwa Ukraine bwo kubaho nk’igihugu ufatiye kuri kahise
 Igihe Uburusiya butera iki gihugu kibanyi ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), Putin yavuga ko cari “igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare” cariko kibera gusa mu karere ka Donbas mu buseruko, mu ntumbero yo “kurwanya ivyiyumviro vy’iki Nazi” muri Ukraine no kugabanya ibishobora kubangamira ubusugire bw’Uburusiya
 Ariko, mu gihe gusa yariko avuga aya majambo, ingabo ziwe zariko zirasatira umugwa mukuru Kyiv, zicucagira n’amabombe irya n’ino gushika no mu burengero
 Inyuma y’imisi irenga 100, ica gatanu c’ubutaka bwa Ukraine buri mu minwe y’igisirikare c’Uburusiya, cashinze mbere n’ubutegetsi bugendera ku mategeko ya Moscou ata kindi bushira imbere atari amatora ya kamarampaka yo kwinjira mu Burusiya
 Hanyuma ubu, Putin yumva afise inguvu zihagije zo kwemeza ko “igikorwa” ciwe mu bisanzwe ari ukwigarurira ubutaka
 Asa kandi n’uwudakekeranya ko impera n’imperuka ibihugu vy’Uburengero bizoruhira kwemera ukuri ingabo ziwe ziriko zirarwanira
 Putin avuga ko ico gihe ata “gihugu na kimwe c’Ubulaya” caha nirwere Uburusiya ku ntambara yo kwigarurira ubutaka Pierre yahavuye ashingamwo St Petersburg nk’umugwa mukuru mushasha w’Uburusiya
 Ariko ubu vyose biremera
 Amajambo yiwe kandi yashavuje ibihugu vyo mu karere ka Baltique
