Intambara zasubiye kwaduka kuva mu gaturuturu ko kuri uno wa Mungu mu gace ka Bunagana kari mu ka karere Rutshuru mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru hagati igisirikare ca Congo, FARDC, n’umuhari wn’inyeshamba M23
 Amakuru ava i Bunagana avuga ko abanyagihugu bahungira muri Uganda no mu tundi duce turimwo umutekano
 Amakuru ava muri Congo avuga ko intambara ziriko zibera mu duce twa Chanzu, Runyoni, bigega, Musongati, Muhenzi na Kariba, nkuko vyemezwa n’umuvugizi wa M23
 Général de Brigade Sylvain Ekenge, umuvugizi wa Buramatari w’intara ya Kivu ya Ruguru, yabwiye BBC ko kuva mu gaturuturu ingabo za Congo zatewe n’inyeshamba za M23
 Avuga ati: “Nagomba nsubire ndabahe amakuru nyayo: igisirikare c’u Rwanda nico giha M23 ibirwanisho rutura hamwe n’ingabo zaco”
 “Inyeshamba za M23 nta birwanisho bikomeye canke birasa kure bafise, ni igisirikare c’u Rwanda cinjiye iwacu, uko cakoze i Kibumba niko kiriko kirabikora na hano i Bunagana, muri kano kanya turiko turavugana intambara zirabandanya kuva mu gaturuturu ko kuri uno wa Mungu”
 U Rwanda rwama ruriyamiriza ivyo rwagirizwa
 Gen, Ekenge we avuga ko iki gihugu kibanyi kidashobora kwemera ibi, akavuga ko bafise ivyemezo vyose vyerekana ko rufise uruhara rukomeye mu ndyane zibera muri ico gihugu
 Ati: “Twebwe turiko turwana n’u Rwanda, rero turashaka ko u Rwanda rwemeza ku mugaragaro ko rudutera,  rugatangaza intambara ku mugaragaro, gutyo tukarwana intambara yeruye n’u Rwanda”
 Umuvugizi w’umuhari M23 Willy Ngoma yamirira kure ibivugwa na reta ya Congo ko ari wo watanguye intambara uyu musi, akavuga ko ingabo za FARDC ziri kumwe n’inyeshamba za FDLR zateye ibirindiro vyazo hanyuma nazo zikivuna
 Anavuga ko bahavuye bafashwa n’ingabo za MONUSCO zarungitswe kubungabunga amahoro muri ako karere
 Ati: “Hafi isaha 5h30, FARDC iri kumwe na FDLR baduteye, batereye rimwe ibirindiro vyacu hanyuma turivuna turabirukana”
 “MONUSCO nayo yaje kubafasha kuva isaha 10h25 baza kudutera na kajugujugu zibiri, baratera amabombe birindro vyacu neza na neza i Chanzu”
 Mu gihe bivugwa ko mu karere ka Bunagana intambara zibica bigacika, uyu muvugizi wa M23 avuga ko bobo babandanya biruka kuri FARDC yabateye gushika iyo yaturutse
 Ati: “Twebwe ku rubuga ico dukora ni ugukurikirana umwansi, tubandanya tumwirukako kugira twivune umwansi gushika iyo yaje ava, nico gituma i Bunagana mwumva hari intambara”
 Mu gihe kandi hari amakuru ko M23 ishobora kwigarurira Bunagana, Willy Ngoma avuga ati: “Intumbero yacu si iyo kwigarurira uturere utu canke turiya, ariko kubw’umutekano wacu, bibaye ngombwa ntituzohingitanya gufata uturere  mu ntumbero yo kwikingira no guhasha umwansi”
 Abajijwe amakuru avuga ko bafashwa n’u Rwanda, mu buryo bw’ibikoresho n’abarwanyi, Willy Ngoma yishuye n’agatwengo kenshi avuga ko ibi bivugwa n’igisirikare ca Congo kugira ngo kinyegeze intege nke zaco
 Ati: “Mbega twebwe twotera gute turi kumwe n’u Rwanda? Mu ntumbero iyahe? Oya! Ivyo vyose babivuga kugira ngo banyegeze intege nke zabo kuko bavuze ko baje kuturandura, kudutuza, kurangiza burundu ikibazo ca M23
 Rero baraje kudutera barakubitwa, nico gituma bivugira aya muhe kugira ngo banyegeze intege nke zabo”
 Nayo ku vyerekeye uburyo, Willy Ngoma yemeza ko ibigwanisho vyinshi babikura mu ngabo za reta ya congo zo nyene
 Ati: “U Rwanda ntirwigeze na rimwe rudufasha, nta n’urushinge rwigeze ruduha
 "Twebwe turi abasirikare bavyigiye neza, twari dufise ibirwanisho twahamvye, rero igihe tugarukiye twaciye duhamburura ibirwanisho vyacu
 Hanyuma iyo turiko turarwana na FARDC, barata ibirwanisho tugaca tubitora”
 “Nk’igihe tuja i Rumangabo, twarogeje ububiko bw’ibirwanisho vyabo, vyose turikorera
 “Igihe cose twama tubatwara ibirwanisho
 Rero iyo bavuga ivyo, ni ukubesha kuko bo nyene barazi ko ibirwanisho dukoresha biva iwabo bo nyene, bata ibirwanisho tugaca tubitora, abasirikare babo bo nyene baragurisha ibirwanisho, rero ni bareke kurondera ivyitwazo, ni bahangane n’ikibazo nyaco uko kiri”
 Abajijwe ku mugambi w’amahoro, Willy Ngoma avuga ko biteguye kuja mu biganiro, ariko ko mu butegetsi bwa Congo hari “abantu badashaka amahoro, abantu badakunda igihugu, barajwe ishinga no kwiyegeraniriza ubutunzi, ariko ntibashake ko ingorane ziri muri Congo zitorerwa umuti”
 Izi ntambara zirabandanya mu gihe umuhari M23 wakuwe mu mugambi w’amahoro watanguriye i Nairobi muri Kenya uhuza reta ya DRC n’imihari iyirwanya, reta ikaba iherutse gutangaza ko uyu muhari ari uw’iterabwoba

Ukraine ivuga ko ingabo zababa 10
000 z’igisirikare cayo bamaze gupfira muri ino ntambara kuva igitero c’Uburusiya gitanguye mu mpera z’ukwa kabiri
 Umuhanuzi w’umukuru w’igihugu  Oleksiy Arestovych yatangaje ibi mu kiganiro cacishijwe ku mbuga hwaniro, igihe yari abajijwe igitigiri c’abasirikare Ukraine imaze gutakaza mu misi 100 ya mbere y’intambara – ni ukuvuga, gushika ku wa 03 Ruheshi (6)
 Ukraine ivuga ko itakaza hafi abasirikare 100 bari ku rugamba buri musi, abandi baharurwa mu majana nabo bagakomereka
 Arestovych avuga ko abo Uburusiya bumaze gukataza bobo barenga kure n’iyo incuro zitari nke
 Reta ya Ukraine ivuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya zirenga 30
000 zimaze gupfa, ariko ibitigiri ngereranyo bitangwa n’igendereza ry’Ubwongereza biri hasi – abarenga 15
000
 Intambara yose ya Afghanistan yo kuva mu 1979 gushika 1989 yahitanye ingabo z’icahoze ari Reta zunze Ubumwe z’abasoviyeti zababa 15
000
 Abategetsi b’Uburusiya ntibaratanga igitigiri nyaco ico ari co cose ku vyerekeye n’abo bamaze gutakariza muri iyi ntambara ya Ukraine kuva ku wa 25 Ntwarante (3), aho bavuze ko abasirikare n’intwazangabo 1351 ari bo bari bamaze gupfa
 Igisata ca BBC gikoresha ururimi rw’ikirusiya cemeza ko abasirikare b’Uburusiya 3502 bapfuye – ariko aba bakaba ari babamenyekanye kandi bahamwe mu matongo y’abapfuye
 Perezida Joe Biden wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika avuga ko mugenziwe wa Ukraine Volodymyr Zelensky  atashatse kwumvira Amerika igiye yariko igabisha ko Uburusiya bwariko butegura igitero ku gihugu ciwe
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu gihe yari mu gikorwa co kegeranya uburyo ejo ku wa gatanu, afatira ku mburi z’uko Uburusiya bwoba bwariko butegura igitero, Biden yavuze ati: “Ndazi ko abantu benshi bibaza ko nariko ndashikuza”
 “Ariko nari nzi ko dufise amakuru yose yavyerekana”
 Yongera ko y’uko ata nkeka zari zihari ko umukuru w’igihugu c’Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yariko atera “aja ku mupaka” ariko “Zelensky ntiyashatse kuvyumva, co kimwe n’abanyagihugu benshi”
 “Ndatahura igituma batashatse kuvyumva, ariko yarinjiye”
 Amerika yatanguye kugabisha ko Uburusiya bwariko butegura igitero kuri Ukraine imisi itari mike imbere y’uko Putin atangaza “igikorwa kidasanzwe” kuri iki gihugu ku wa 24 Ruhuruma (2) 
 Izi mburi zafashwe nk’ugushikuza mbere ziranegurwa bikomeye n’ibihugu bimwe bimwe vy’incuti za Amerika i Bulaya, vyafashe ico gihe ko Amerika yariko irashikuza
 Kuva iyi ntambara itanguye, Uburusiya buramaze kwigarurira ibisagara bikeya, ubu ikaba yashize inguvu zose mu buseruko aho iriko irondera kwigarurira intara za Luhansk na Donesk ziri mu karere ka Donbas
 Ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Ubwongereza buvuga ko igisagara ca Severodonetsk kiriko kiberamwo intambara z’urutavanako
 Buvuga ko bisa n’uko impande zompi ziriko ziratakaza igitigiri kinini c’ingabo muri izi ntambara zikomeye zibera ku mabarabara y’ico gisagara
 Hagati aho, ubu bushikiranganji buvuga ko ingabo z’Uburusiya ata ntambwe ziratere utera uja mu bumanuko bw’iki gisagara
 Buvuga kandi ko Uburusiya buriko buregeranya invugu zo hasi no mu kirere kugira ngo bushobore gucuvya burundu ingabo za Ukraine
 Mu buseruko bwa Ukraine, itsinzi ku rugamba ibandanya ironkwa n’uwufise ibikoho binini binini
 Ni vya muzinga n’ibindi birasa ibisasu kure – bishobora gutera ibirindiro vy’umwansi
 Iyi ni intambara – bisa nk’aho – Uburusiya ari bwo bworohewe ubu
 Umwe mu bategetsi bo hejuru mu gisata c’umutekano yabwiye ikinyamakuru co mu Bwongereza, Guardian ko uruhande rwiwe ubu ruriko ruraherezwa n’amasasu
 Vadym Skibitsky avuga ko abarusiya ubu basumvya ibikoresho abanya Ukraine incuro kuva kuri cumi gushika kuri cumi na zitanu, ko rero ingabo za Ukraine zikeneye vuba bwango ibindi bikoresho
 Hari vyinshi bimaze kwemerwa – cane cane vya muzinga bigezweho vyo mu bwoko bwa HIMAR na M270 vyo muri Amerika no mu Bwongereza – ibi bikaba ari ntahusha
 Ariko ntibirashika ku rubuga rw’intambara  igenda iba nabi
 Bimwe mu bisagara biherutse kwigarurirwa n’ingabo z’Uburusiya harimwo Mariupol, igisagara kiri ku nkengera y’inyanja mu bumanuko bushira ubuseruko bwa Ukraine, ubu kikavugwa ko gishobora kwadukamwo ikiza ca cholera, nk’uko bivugwa n’ubushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bw’Ubwongereza
 Inyubakwa hafi zose zo muri iki gisagara zarononekaye canke zirasenyurwa, amazi akaba yavanganye n’imyanda iva mu tuzu twa surwumwe nk’uko bivugwa n’ishirahamwe ONU
 Iki kiza caribonekeje i Mariupol imbere y’aha, kandi abarwayi bakaba baribonekeje irya n’ino mu kwezi guheze
 Umukuru w’igisagara wo ku ruhande rwa Ukraine, Vadym Boychenko, yabwiye BBC ko “cholera, amacinya n’izindi ndwara zandukira zamaze gushika mu gisagara”, kandi ko cugawe kugira ngo ntihaduke akaranda gakomeye
 Aya makuru ntashobora guhinyuzwa na BBC, mbere umukuru w’iki gisagara yagenywe n’Uburusiya avuga ko ibipimo vyama bikorwa igihe cose kandi ko ata muntu n’umwe arwaye cholera arigera aboneka

Igisirikare cy’u Rwanda kivuga ko banyurujwe ku mupaka bari mu kazi kabo ko gukizura
 Igisirikare cya DR Congo kivuga ko bafatiwe hafi y’ikambi ya gisirikare ya Rumangabo mu ntara ya Kivu ya Ruguru ku birometero birenga 20 uvuye ku rubibe rw’u Rwanda
 Aba basirikare bafashwe ku wa 23 Rusama (5) bazwi ku mazina ya Nkundabagenzi Elysee na Ntwari Gad
 Bafashwe mu gihe hari intambara zikomeye hagati y’igisirikare ca Congo (FARDC) hamwe n’inyeshamba z’umuhari M23, reta ya Congo ikagiriza Urwanda ko rufasha uyu muhari watangajwe ko ari uw'iterabwoba, ivyo ruhakana
 Itangazo rihejeje gusohorwa n’igisirikare c’u Rwanda rivuga riti: “Inyuma y’inyuruzwa ry’abasirikare babiri ba RDF bariko barakizura ku rubibe hagati y’u Rwanda na DRC ku wa 23 Rusama 2022, n’ibiganiro vyakurikiye hagati y’abakuru b’ibihugu vya Angola, DRC n’u Rwanda, RDF iri n’munezero wo kumenyesha ko aba basirikare babiri bagarukanywe neza mu Rwanda
 “RDF irashima utwigoro twakozwe kugira ngo izi ngabo zayo zibiri zirekurwe”
 Ifatwa rya Kaporari Nkundabagenzi Elysee na Private Ntwari Gad ryashingiweko n'igisirikare ca DR Congo, nk'ikimenyetso c’ivyo bagiriza u Rwanda ko rwinjiye muri ico gihugu gufasha M23
 Reta y’u Rwanda irahakana yivuye inyuma ivyo yagirizwa, ahubwo ikagiriza igisirikare ca Congo ko gikorana n'umuhari FDLR wagirizwa ihonyabwoko ryo mu Rwanda mu 1994 mu guhingabanya iki gihugu
 Reta y’u Rwanda yabandanije isaba ko yosubizwa abasirikare bayo bari mu minwe ya Congo
 Vyabaye ngombwa ko Perezida wa Angola João Lourenço aja hagati, ari ho mu ntango z’uku kwezi Perezida Felix Tshisekedi yemeye kubakura, hari mu nama yabahuje kuwa kabiri i Luanda, nk'uko vyatangajwe n'itororokanirizo ry’amakuru rya reta ya Angola, Angop

Igisirikare ca Repubulika y’Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo (FARDC) be n'ic’u Rwanda (RDF) vyagirizanya guterana amabombe  ejo ku wa gatanu
 Itangazo ryasohowe n’umuvugizi wa buramatari w’intara ya Kivu ya Ruguru rivuga ko amabombe cumi avuye mu Rwanda yahitanye abana babiri umwe w’imyaka indwi uwundi w’imyaka itandatu, bikomeretsa uwundi umwe
 Iri tangazo ryasohowe haciye umwanya muto igisirikare c’u Rwanda naco gisohoye itangazo ryaco, aho cagiriza ingabo za Congo ko “zarashe amaroketi abiri ya 122mm ku butaka bw’u Rwanda akagwa mu kigwati ca Nyabigoma, muri Umurenve wa Kinigi iri mu karere ka Musanze”
 “Nta bakomeretse canke ngo bahasige ubuzima, ariko abanyagihugu b’ako karere batekewe n’ubwoba”, nk’uko tubisoma muri iri tangazo ry’igisirikare c’u Rwanda
 U Rwanda ruvuga ko ibi bisasu bisa n’ivyarashwe “n’ingabo za DRC ku wa 19 na 23 Ntwarante [3] mu ma segiteri ya Kinigi na Nyange mu karere ka Musanze be no mu murenge wa Gahunga mu karere ka Burera, bikaba vyarakomerekeje abantu vyonona n’ibintu”
 Ku ruhande rwa DR Congo, Jenerali Ekenge Sylvain, umuvugizi wa buramatari wa Kivu ya Ruguru, avuga ko ibiri muri iri tangazo rya RDF ari urwitwazo mu kurondera “kwihora abanyagihugu bafashije gufata ingabo zidasanzwe z’igisirikare c’u Rwanda”, aha u Rwanda rukaba ruvuga ko bafatiwe ku butaka bwarwo bari mu bikorwa vyo gukizura
 Ati: “Ariko kandi mu kuyovya no guhenda amakungu ku migambi yarwo y’intambara, u Rwanda rwasohoye itangazo rivuga ko ingabo za FARDC zoba zateye amabombe ku butaka bw’u Rwanda
 Niyo mayeri yakoreshejwe mu bitero biheruka i Rumangabo na Kubumba
 Umuvugizi wa Buramatari wa Kivu ya Ruguru, avuga kandi ko bafise amasanamu ya za ndege zitagira abadereva (drones) yerekana ko ingabo z’u Rwanda zigaruriye uduce twa Tchanzu na Runyoni mu mugambi wo gufata mu mugongo za nyeshamba za M23
 Icuka si ciza hagati y’u Rwanda na DR Congo, ibintu bikaba vyagiye kwunyuka kuva mu misi mike iheze hadutse intambara hagati y’igisirikare ca Congo n’umuhari w’inyeshamba M23, Congo ikagiriza u Rwanda ko rushigikiye uyu muhari
 Ku ruhande rw’u Rwanda, reta ivuga ko ata ruhara na ruto ifise muri iyo ntambara, ikagiriza ahubwo igisirikare ca Congo kwifatanya n’umuhari w’inyeshamba FDLR mu kurondera guhungabanya u Rwanda

Sentare nkuru yafashe ingingo ko urugendo rw’indege itegekanijwe gukura abasaba ubuhungiro mu Bwongereza ibatwara mu Rwanda ku wa kabiri rubandanya ukuri kwaye
 Abarwanya uwu mugambi bananiwe mu rugamba rwa mbere rwo guhagarika uwu mugambi wo kurungika abantu mu Rwanda, ariko bemeza ko bazokwungururiza urubanza muri sentare y’iyungururizo ku wa mbere
 Muri uwu mugambi, bamwe mu binjira mu Bwogereza badakurikije amategeko bazokwungururirzwa mu Rwanda kugira ngo basabeyo ubuhungiro
 Abashika 31 niba bamaze kubwirwa ko bazokwurizwa iyi ndege ya mbere
 Hazoba umwihwezo wimbitse aho sentare nkuru y’igihugu izokwumviriza ibishikirizwa n’abarwanya uwu mugambi muri rusangi imbere y’impera za Mukakaro (7)
