 Abarenga 10
000 nibo bafashe uru rugendo rwo mu mazi ruteye ubwoba muri uno mwaka gushika ubu
 Abarwanya uwu mugambi bari barondeye guhagarika urugendo rw’iyi ndege izokwunguruza aba bantu
 Urubanza rwashinzwe n’abashingwamanza baserukira aba basaba ubuhungiro bitezwe kurungikwa mu Rwanda, hamwe na sendika  Public and Commercial Services union (PCS) – iserukira abarenga 80% y’abakozi bose b’igisata c’Ubwongereza kijejwe imbibe – hamwe n’amashirahamwe yitaho abimukira Care4Calais na Detention Action
  Abanyamategeko bayo berekana impungenge bafise ku bijanye n’utunenge turi mu ntunganyo y’igisata kijejwe impunzi mu Rwanda be n’uko bishoboka ko abantu bashobora kurungikwa mu bihugu bashobora gutoterezwamo – ico bita kwirukana (refoulement)
 Abanyamategeko b’Ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati mu Bwongereza babwiye sentare ko umugambi udashobora guhagarikwa n’abawurwanya baciye muri sentare kubera ari ku nyungu z‘igihugu, baca basaba kandi umucamanza gutesha agaciro ibirego bishikirizwa kw’izina ry’abasaba ubuhungiro ku giti cabo
 Muri urwo rubanza, ishami rya ONU ryitaho impunzi, UNHCR, naryo nyene ryamenyesheje ko ryitandukanije n’uwu mugambi
 Abashingwamanza ba UNHCR bavuga kandi ko bagabishije ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati ko iyi nteguro n’Urwanda iteye kubiri n’amategeko
 Mu ngingo yiwe, umucamanza Swift yatesheje agaciro ibirego vy’abashaka guhagarika vy’agateganyo indege zizokwunguruza aba bantu imbere y’uko uru rubanza rwihwezwa neza muri Mukakaro
 Avuga ko atigeze abona ko hari ibimenyetso vyerekana ko hashobora kuba "ihohotera, ukwirukanwa” canke ikindi kintu cose kibangamira uburenganzira bwabo nk'uko biri mu ngingo ya gatatu y'itegeko ryerekeye uburenganzira bwa muntu mu Bwongereza
 Ingingo ya gatatu ikingira abantu iyicarubozo, gufatwa nabi nk’ikiremwamuntu, no kwirukanwa canke kurungikwa mu gihugu aho bishobora gushika umuntu akaborezwa igufa canke agafatwa nabi
 Umucamanza Swift avuga ko bimwe mu birego bitangwa n’abashaka kuzibira izi ndege za mbere bivuga cane cane ko ingingo ya Patel “yo gufata Urwanda nk’igihugu gitekanye idafise ishingiro kandi ko ishingiye ku matohoza adakwiye”
 Avuga ko iki kirego, co kimwe n’ibindi biri muri uru rubanza, bishobora kwigirwa hamwe n’ivyemezo mu gihe iyi ngingo izokwihwezwa mu buryo bwimbitse  - mu kiringo c’imisi ibiri imbere y’uko ukw’indwi kurangira
 Ariko, umucamanza Swift asigura ko, n’aho abarwanya uwu mugambi bari bafise ivyemezo bihagije vy’uko uwu mugambi wokwihwezwa neza, ivyo bavuga “si ibintu bikomeye cane”
 Inyuma y’iyi ngingo ya sentare, umushikiranganji Patel yavuze ko reta “izobandanya” n’uwu mugambi
 Avuga ati: “Abantu bazoguma bagerageza kurondera no guhagarika irungikwa ryabo bifashishije amasentare n’ibibazo baserura ku munota wa nyuma, ariko ntiturora dutezura mu guhagarika iyi magendo y’abantu ihitana abatari bake no mu kurokora ubuzima
 “U Rwanda ni igihugu gitekanye kandi giherutse no kwizerwa ko gitanga ubuhungiro bwiza – tuzobandanya twitegurira urugendo rwa mbere rugana mu Rwanda, hamwe n’izindi ngingo zose zitari nke zifise intumbero yo kugabanya amato mato mato yinjira”
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Jonhson yacishije ubutumwa bwiwe ku rubuga rwa Twitter avuga ati: “Ntidushobora kwemera ko abakora magendo y’abantu bata mu kaga ubuzima kandi incuti zacu kw’isi zizofasha mu guhagarika uru rudandaza rw’izi nkozi z’ikibi ruburakigongwe”
 James Wilson, icegera c’ishirahamwe Detention Action rirwanya uwu mugambi, avuga ko yababajwe n’iyi ngingo
 Clare Moseley, yatanguje Care4Calais avuga ko ishirahamwe ryiwe “rifise impungenge nyinshi ku bijanye n’imibereho y’abantu bashobora gutwarwa ku nguvu mu Rwanda, ingingo ishobora kubangamira cane ubuzima bwabo bwo mu mutwe na kazoza”
 Inyuma y’iyi ngingo ya sentare, sendika PCS isaba ko hoba ibiganiro vyihuta n’umushikiranganji Patel kugira ngo bihweze uwu mugambi wo kwimura abantu

Umuhanuzi wo mu rwego rwo hejuru wa prezida wa Ukraine yabwiye BBC ko abasirikare ba Ukraine bari hagati ya 100 na 200 bicirwa ku rubuga rw'intambara buri musi
 Mykhaylo Podolyak yavuze ko Ukraine ikeneye amajana n'amajana y'ibigwanisho bikomakomeye mu kwongereza ubushobozi ku rubuga rw'intambara ibahuza n'Uburusiya mu karere ko mu buseruko ka Donbas
 Yavuze kandi ko Ukraine ititeguye gusubira mu biganiro vy'amahoro n'Uburusiya
 Ingabo za Ukraine ziriko ziraterwa amabombe urutitsa mu gihe ingabo z'Uburusiya ziriko ziragerageza kwigarurira akarere kose ka Donbas
 Podolyak agira ati: "Ingabo z'Uburusiya zikoresha ikintu cose uretse ibigwanisho vy'ubumara ku rugamba, harimwo n'ibikoho bikomakomeye, ibikoho bitera za rokete hamwe n'indege
" Yasubiyemwo akamo ka Ukraine ku bihugu vya Buraya ko gusaba ibindi bigwanisho vyinshi, avuga ko "ubusumbane bukomeye" hagati y'igisirikare c'Uburusiya n'ica Ukraine, ari yo mpamvu haba abapfa benshi ku ruhande rwa Ukraine
 Yavuze "ugusaba ibigwanisho bikomeye si ukwigirisha


 ariko n'intumbero dukeneye gushikako uravye uko ibintu vyifashe ku rubuga
" Yongeyeko yuko Ukraine ikeneye ibigwanisho bitera rokete nyinshi ica rimwe biri hagati ya 150 na 300 kugira babangabanganwe n'Uburusiya - igitigiri kinini batari bwigere baronka gushika ubu
 Podolyak yavuze kandi ko ibiganiro vy'amahoro bishobora gusubira mu gihe gusa Uburusiya busubije uturere bwigaruriye kuva buteye ico gihugu itariki 24 z'ukwezi kwa kabiri
 Igitigiri c'abasirikare bari hagati 100 na 200 ba Ukraine bapfa buri musi kiri hejuru cane n'ivyahora bigereranywa
 Ku musi wa kane, umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi, Oleksii Reznikov, yavuze ko Ukraine ibura abasirikare 100 buri musi, abandi 500 bagakomereka
 Uko gutanga ibiharuro bitandukanye vyerekana ingene bitoroshe kuronka inkuru nyazo ziva ku rugamba
 Uretse uko gutakaza abantu benshi, Reznikov yemeza ko igitigiri kinini c'abasirikare na bo bicwa
 Reznikov agira ati: "Uburusiya bubandanya guhangana n'abantu benshi n'inguvu nyinshi kandi buratakaza abantu benshi
" "Ariko buguma bufise inguvu zo gutera intambwe ku rugamba mu turere tumwe tumwe
" Muri ico gihe nyene, umukuru w'intara ya Luhansk yavuze ko abarusiya "bariko barapfa nk'isazi" ariko akanasubiramwo ivyavuzwe na Podolyak ko Ukraine ihanganye  n'ingorane "zikomeye cane" z'ibura ry'ibirwanisho bikomakomeye
 Abarusiya bariko bashira inguvu nyinshi mu bitero vyo ku gisagara ca Severodonetsk
 Ku musi wa gatatu, prezida Zelensky yavuze ko "kazoza ka Donbas kariko kararondererwa ngaho" kandi abategetsi bavuga ko iyo ntara yahinduwe umunyota n'ibitero bikomeye vy'Uburusiya vyiganjemwo za Misile
 Kuri izo ntambara, hiyongeyeko abagwanyi b'abongereza babiri hamwe n'umunye Maroc bagwana ku ruhande rw'igisirikare ca Ukraine baciriwe urubanza rwo gupfa ku musi wa kane na sentare itemewe n'amakungu y'iciyita Republica y'abanyagihugu ya Donetsk
 Bagiriwe n'icaha co kuba abacangero no "gufata ibigwanisho bagamije gufata ubutegetsi ku nguvu
"
Sentare nkuru y'Ubwongereza yabwiwe ko ishami rya ONU rijejwe impunzi kw'isi, HCR, ryagabishije incuro zibiri ubushikiranganji bw'intwaro yo hagati mu gihugu ko amasezerano bagiraniye n'Urwanda yo kurungika abasaba ubuhungiro muri ico gihugu adakurikije amategeko
 Umushingwamanza w'iryo shirahamwe yavuze ivyo igihe hariko haraba urubanza rugamije kubuza ko ayo masezerano ashirwa mu ngiro
 Abashingwamanza b’ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati mu gihugu mu Bwongereza bavuze ko umugambi wo kurungika mu Rwanda abarondera ubuhungiro  udashobora guhagarikwa n’abawugwanya bishimikije amategeko – kubera uri mu nyungu z’abanyagihugu
 Reta ishaka guca intege abantu bajabuka Manche baja kurondera ubuhungiro mu gutomora ko menshi mu madosiye yabo azokwigirwa mu Rwanda
 Mu ntahe yo muri sentare, abo bashingwamanza basavye umucamanza kudaha agaciro ibirego vyashikirijwe sentare kw’izina ry’umwe umwe ku basaba ubuhungiro
 Abantu bashika 100 babwiwe ko bashobora kurungikwa mu ndege ya mbere, ku wa kabiri itariki 14 Ruheshi (6)
 Imbere y’uko iyo ntahe itangura, vyamenyekanye ko nibura abantu batatu babwiwe ko batakiri ku rutonde rw’abazotwarwa n’iyo ndege
 Iyo ntahe ishingiye ku mwumvikano w’ubushikiranganji bw’intwaro yo hagati mu gihugu n’Urwanda wo kurungika muri ico gihugu bamwe mu barondera ubuhungiro  kugirango amadosiye yabo abe ari ho yigirwa – mu gihe mu nzira yabo yo kuja mu Bwongereza, baba baraciye mu kindi gihugu gitekanye bari kuba barondeyemwo ubuhungiro
 Mu gihe dosiye yabo izoba iriko irigirwa mu Rwanda, bazohabwa aho baba kandi bafashwe, bigenze neza, bashobore kuguma baba mu Rwanda bafashwa kwiga no gushigikirwa mu kiringo c’imyaka itanu
 Abo amadosiye yabo atazokwemerwa mu Rwanda bazohabwa amahirwe yo gusaba uburenganzira bwo kwinjira (visa) biciye mu zindi nzira n'iba bashaka kuguma muri ico gihugu, ariko kandi bazoba bashobora no kwirukanwa
 Mu ngiro, uwo mugambi werekeye abajabuka baciye  muri Manche, ubu bagereranywa ku 10
000 uyu mwaka
 Mu nyandiko zashikirijwe sentare nkuru, abo bashingwamanza bavuze bati: “Kubarungika mu Rwanda biciye mu masezerano yo gufashanya mu vy’ubutunzi n’iterambere [n’Urwanda] hisunzwe ingingo zo kutemerwa zo mu mategeko yo kwinjira mu gihugu, kugamije ineza ikomeye y’abanyagihugu
 “Kuvana abantu mu Bwongereza bigamije guca intege abantu biheba mu gufata ingendo zo kuza mu Bwongereza kurondera ubuhungiro, babifashijwemwo n’inkozi z’ikibi zinjiza abantu mu kinyegero, kandi baba bamaze guca mu kindi gihugu gitekanye
 “Bw’umwihariko, ariko atari abo gusa, ivyo bigamije guca intege abashika baje mu bwato buto buto
” Urubanza rwashingishirijwe ubushikiranganji n’urunani rw’abaharanira uburenganzira rufise intambwe zibiri
 Ubwa mbere  bashaka  kubuza ko hajanwa mu Rwanda abantu bamaze kumenyeshwa ko bazorungikwa
 Ubwa kabiri bashaka guhinyuza niba  irungikwa iryari ryo ryose rihuye n’amategeko
 Raza Hussain QC, aserukira bamwe muri abo bashingishije urubanza, yabwiye sentare ko ishami rya ONU riraba impunzi (UNHCR) ritewe impungenge n’ibibura mu ndinganizo y’ugusaba ubuhungiro mu Rwanda
 Yavuze ko mu biteye impungenge HCR harimwo ivyemeza ko abasaba ubuhungiro bashobora kwimwa urubanza, umushingwamanza n’uwuhindura indimi - kandi ko bashobora gusanga barungitswe mu bihugu bikora ivyo kuboreza igufa abantu
 ONU ntirashobora gukurikirana neza ubuziranenge bw’ingene ingingo zifatwa muri ico gihugu n’ubwo umushikiranganji w’intwaro yo hagati Priti Patel yemeje ko Urwanda rutekanye, nk’uko yavuze
 Hussain yabandanije ati: “Aya n’amakenga yashikirijwe reta y’Ubwongereza ariko gushika ubu reta aho ihagaze n’uko ONU yemeye ko uwo mugambi ubandanya
 Ivyo bavuga si vyo
 “Ivyo si vyo bibonwa n’ishirahamwe ritegamiye reta ryubashwe - ni ibibonwa na HCR kandi bitegerezwa guhabwa uburemere
” Uwo mushingwamanza yashimangiye ko HCR ifise inshingano zo gucungera [amategeko mpuzamakungu agenga impunzi] no kuba umuhinga muri ico gisata
 Yavuze ati: “Ntituri ku rubuga mu Rwanda, umushikiranganji ntari ku rubuga mu Rwanda,” yongerako ati: “HCR yo ni ho iri
 Vyoshoboka gute kurungikayo abantu HCR yavuze uko?” Laura Dubinsky QC, aserukira HCR, yabwiye sentare ati “kubera hari ibintu bivugwa ukutari ko” ashaka gutomora ko iryo shami rya ONU ritigeze rishigikira uwo mwumvikano w’Ubwongereza n’Urwanda
 Yavuze ko HCR yabwiye umushikiranganji ko uwo mwumvikano udahuye n’amategeko
