Ikigo cerekana za filime co mu Bwongereza, Cineworld, cahagaritse kwerekana mu mazu ya filime (cinema) yaco yose muri ico gihugu filime ivuga ku mukobwa w'umuhanuzi w'idini rya Islamu, Muhammad, nyuma y'imyiyerekano yadutse hanze y'ama-cinema amwe amwe
 Ico kigo ca cinema cavuze yuko cafashe iyo ngingo "ku bw'umutekano w'abakozi n'abakiriya bacu"
 Abantu barenga 120
000 bashize umukono ku nyandiko isaba ko filime yitwa The Lady of Heaven (Umudamu w'Ijuru) itokwerekanwa muri za cinema zo mu Bwongereza
 Ihuriro ry'imisigiti, The Bolton Council of Mosques, ryavuze ko iyo filime ari sakirirego kandi irimwo amacakubiri afatiye kw'idini
 Ariko umukenguzamateka Baroness Claire Fox yavuze ko iyo ngingo "ari icago ku bugenegene kandi ikaba ari mbi cane ku bwigenge bwo gushikiriza iciyumviro"
 Nayo umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza ajejwe amagara y'abantu, Sajid Javid, yavuze yuko "atewe umwitwarariko cane n'umuco wo kwiyamiriza uriko uragwirirana" mu Bwongereza
 Iyo filime yakuwe mu bigo vya cinema vy'ikigo Cineworld nyuma y'amakuru y'imyiyerekano mu miji wa Bolton, Birmingham na Sheffield
 I Bolton, abantu barenga ijana bagize imyiyerekano hanze ya cinema, nk'uko vyatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru caho, Bolton News
 Mu butumwa bwa email bugenewe Cineworld bwashizwe ahabona na Bolton News, umukuru w'urwego Bolton Council of Mosques, Asif Patel, yavuze ko iyo filime "irimwo ingengabitekerezo y'amacakubiri afatiye ku dini" kandi yuko "ivuga ukutari ko kahise k'idini ikanasuzuguza icubahiro Islamu ihabwa n'amateka yayo"
 Igitangazamakuru cegamiye idini rya Islamu co kuri internet, 5Pillars, catangaje kuri Twitter amafoto y'abo cavuze ko ari aba-Islamu 200, bari mu myiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza iyo filime imbere y'inyubakwa ya Cineworld i Birmingham ku munsi wa Mungu
 Video yahanahanywe kuri internet isa n'iyerekana umuyobozi w'inyubakwa ya Cineworld i Sheffield ariko arabwira abari mu myiyerekano ko iyo filime yahagaritswe kwerekanwa, nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikinyamakuru Guardian
 BBC ntibazwa ibivuye ku zindi mbuga Umuhinguzi mukuru (executive producer) ari mu bateguye iyi filime, Malik Shlibak, yabariye BBC ko abari mu myiyerekano bigenza "nk'amabandi arenganya abandi, bakisuka muri za cinema banatera ubwoba abahakora"
 "Ibi ni ibintu bitari bikwiye kwihanganirwa mu Bwongereza", nk'uko yabandanije avuga, aca agabisha yuko guhagarika kwerekana iyi filime bizoha ingoga abakoresha ukwiyamiriza nk'uko muri kazoza
 Yabandanije agira ati "ibi birarengeye filime
 Uno munsi hifatiwe mu gahanga filime Lady of Heaven, ejo harashobora kwiyamirizwa ikindi kigushika ku mutima kurusha"
 Yavuze kandi yuko abakora imyiyerekano batazoshobora kubuza kubaho kw'iyi filime

Umugore w’umunyamerika yemeye ko yari arongoye ibatayo (bataillon) yari igizwe n’abagore gusa mu muhari wiyita Reta ya ki-Islam (Etat Islamique/Islamic State, IS) muri Syria, kandi ko yanateguye n’ibitero ku butaka bwa Amerika
 Allison Fluke-Ekren yemeye icaha kimwe co gufasha uyu muhari, yongera yemera ko yigishije ubukozi bw’ikibi abagore n’abakobwa barenga 100
 Uyu muvyeyi akongera akaba n’umwigisha yahindutse akaba indongozi muri IS yavuye muri Amerika mu 2011, akaba yabanje gukorana n’umurwi w’iterabwoba muri Libya imbere y’uko aja muri Syria
 Mu rubanza rutegekanywa gusomwa muri Gitugutu (10), ashobora gucirirwa umunyororo wo gushika ku myaka 20
 Fluke-Ekren w’imyaka 42, yahoze yiga ivyigwa ndondabuzima (biologie) mbere akanavyigisha, yafashe urugendo rwamushikanye muri Syria kugira yinjire muri uwu muhari inyuma yo kuba mu Misiri no muri Turukiya
 Amaze gushika muri IS, yarongoye Khatiba Nusaybah, ibatayo yari igizwe n’abagore gusa yari mu cafatwa nk’umugwa mukuru Raqqa muri Syria
 Amabanga nyamukuru yiwe kwari ukwigisha abagore n’abakobwa gukoresha inkoho, kuva ku nkoho za AK-47 (Kalachnikov) n’amagerenade gushika ku mikanda y’ubwiyahuzi (suicide vests/ceintures d’explosifs), nk’uko abategetsi babivuga
 Imbere ya sentare yo muri Virginia ejo ku wa kabiri, yaremeye ko yigishije iyi batayo yari igizwe n’abagore gusa, ariko ko atigeze agerageza kwinjiza abana mu vya gisirikare
 Imboneshakure CNN imusubiramwo avuga ati: “Ntitwigeze dushaka kwigisha abakobwa bakiri bato”
 Bamwe mu bagore yigishije biteze kumwagiriza mu gihe azoba arengukishijwe
 Fluke-Ekren yari azwi ku ritazirano rya Umm Mohammed al-Amriki yarabaye kandi i Mosul muri Irak inyuma y’aho iki gisagara cigaruriwe n’abarwanyi ba IS
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’abashikirizamanza, umwe mu bo yigisha avuga urwanko yari agezeko  rwari “rurenze urugero”
 Yemeza kandi ko yavuganye n’abandi ku kungene bokora ibitero ku butaka bwa Amerika, harimwo kw’ishure kaminuza be no mu kigo c’idandarizo (centre commercial/shopping mall)
 “Yabona ko igitero ico ari co cose kidahitanye igitigiri kinini c’abantu caba ari impfagusa”, nk’uko bivugwa n’icabona
 Inzandiko kandi zivuga ko umugabo wiwe wa kabiri yari uwo mu murwi Ansar Al-Sharia, , umuhari w’inyeshamba ziyitirira idini rya Islam wateye urupangu rwa Amerika i Benghazi muri Libya mu 2012
 We n’umugabo wiwe yahavuye yicirwa mu gitero c’indege, barakoze icegeranyo bagihereza abategetsi b’uyu muhari bamaze kwihweza inzandiko za Amerika zafatiwe muri ico gitero ca Benghazi
 Muri sentare, yarakoroye amosozi abajijwe n’umucamanza nimba yemeye iki caha kubera igitigiri kinini c’abana biwe
 Abanyamuryango biwe barigeze gusaba sentare ko yomubuza kuvugana nabo
 Nk’uko bivugwa n’umushikirizamanza umwe wa Amerika, izi ncuti zivuga ko yasize “iharama ry’ubuhemu” kandi ko bashobora no gusohora amatangazo amwiyamiriza mu gihe azoba asomerwa urubanza ku wa 25 gitugutu

Japhet Ndabagiriye yaminuje mu bwubatsi, ariko yorora amafi i Bujumbura aciye ku bundi bworozi butamenyerewe cane
 Avuga ko agiheza amashure yaronse akazi ko kwubaka ariko kakamuruhisha kandi agahembwa make cane
 Yigira umugambi wo kworora amafi, ashinga ishirahamwe AKEZA Village Fermier rikorera muri Zone Kinama yo muri komine Ntahangwa mu gisagara ca Bujumbura
 Mu kuzigaburira, yaciye atangura kworora isazi n'imisiba (iminyorogoto mu Kinyarwanda)
 Ndabagiriye avuga ko ubwo bworozi bworoshe cane
 Ati: "Kworora isazi biroroshe kuko bitwara ikibanza gito
 "Uvanga amase y'ingurube n'ay'inka ukongeramwo ibintu bimota bihamagara isazi, ugaca ushira ahantu hitwa mu mitego
 Aho niho isazi zita amagi
 Ayo magi aca avamwo ibinyagu "duca tuguma tugaburira ivyamwa gushika  bikure
" "Ivyo binyagu vy'isazi n'imisiba ni vyo duheza tukagaburira amafi"
 Japhet Ndabagiriye avuga ko imisiba na yo ayororera mu bisandugu
 Agira ati: "Dufata umwavuye usanzwe tukawurenza ku mufuko urimwo amayezi n'ubuseri bivanze
 "Inyuma y'imisi indwi, imisiba iba yabonetse
 "Duca tuyunguruza tukayishira mw'ivu risanzwe, tukaza turayigaburira imicafu isanzwe iva mu mazu, nk'ibishishwa vy'amavoka


 "Turaheza kandi tukayipfukisha ikintu kubera ikunda ahantu hari umwijima
" Japhet Ndabagiriye avuga ko ubwo buhinga yagiye arabwiyigisha wenyene ku mbuga hwaniro
 Ati: "Naja kuri YouTube nkaraba uko urundi rwaruka rw'ahandi ruvyifatamwo mu kworora amafi
" Amaze kubimenya, yararonse n'akaryo ko gukarisha ubwenge mu bindi bihugu
 Avuga ko ubu afasha mu gukarihiriza ubwenge urundi rwaruka mu vyerekeye kworora amafi agaburirwa ibinyagu vy'isazi n'imisiba
 Asaba urundi rwaruka gufata umwanya mu kwiyigisha ku mbuga hwaniro
 Uwo musore w'imyaka 33, avuga ko asarura amafi buri mezi atandatu
 Ikiro c'amafi  kigurwa ibihumbi umunani vy'amarundi, ko rero ashobora kuronka nk'imiriyoni umunani ku kinogo kimwe yasaruye
 Japhet Ndabagiriye ati: "Mu kinogo kimwe nshobora gukuramwo ibiro 800 canke itoni
"
Uwuserukira Uburusiya muri ONU yivumbuye mu mubonano w’Inama nkuru ya ONU ijejwe umutekano kw’isi inyuma y’uko umukuru w’Inama nkuru y’Ubumwe bwa Bulaya avugiye ko igitero c’Uburusiya kuri Ukraine ari co giteje ikibazo c’imfungurwa kw’isi
 Charles Michel avuga ko Uburusiya bukoresha imfungurwa “nka misire mbi” ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y’amajambere, bigatuma baterwa n’ubukene
 Intumwa y’ Uburusiya Vassily Nebenzia yagirije Michel ko akwiragiza ibinyoma
 Intambara yatumye imfungurwa zugaranirwa ku bivuka vya Ukraine
 Ukraine ni igihugu gishora hanze amavuta yo guteka menshi co kimwe n’intete, nk’ibigori n’ingano
 Uburusiya na bwo nyene burashora hanze ingano nyinshi hamwe n’intabire
 Ubukene bw’ibi bidandazwa bwatumye ibiciro vy’ibibisubirira biduga cane
 Muri uwo mubonano w’Inama Nkuru ijejwe umutekano mw’ishirahamwe ONU i New York, Michel yavuze ati: “Nyakwubahwa Ambasaderi yUburusiya, reka tuvugishe ukuri, Kremlin iriko ikoresha ikibazo c’imfungurwa nka misire mbi ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y’amajambere
 “Ingaruka mbi z’intambara y’Uburusiya ziriko zirarenga inkombe kw’isi yose kandi ibi biriko bituma ibiciro vy’imfungurwa biduga, bigatuma abantu binjira mu bukene, mbere bigateza umutekano muke mu burere
 “Uburusiya bwonyene ni bwo ntanduruko y’iki kibazo c’imfungurwa”
 Yongerako kandi ko yiboneye we nyene ubwiwe amamiriyoni y’amatoni y’ingano zugaraniwe ku kivuko ca Odesa kubera Uburusiya bwazibiye imihora ya Ukraine yo ku nyanja
 Michel kandi yagirije Uburusiya kwiba intete ikanabuza abanyagihugu gutera ibiterwa be no kwimbura ivyimburwa muri Ukraine kubera ibikorwa vya gisirikare vyabwo muri ico gihugu
 Aya majambo yatumye Nebenzia yivumbura
 Ariko arasohoka, Michel yamubwiye imbonankubone ati: “Urashobora gusohoka, kumbure biroroshe kutumviriza ukuri”
 Nebenzia yabwiye Reuters ko atashobora kugumayo kubera “ibinyoma Charles Michel yaje gushikiriza hano”
 Mu nama yindi, umunyamabanga wa Reta ya Amerika ajejwe imigenderanire, Antony Blinken, na we nyene yavuze ko Uburusiya bubuza Ukraine gushora intete hanze, yongera yagiriza ingabo z’Uburusiya gusambura uburimyi bw Ukraine
 Mw’ijambo yashikirije mu nama yabaye hakoreshejwe ubuhinga bwa none yahuje abagiraneza, amashirahamwe ategamiye reta hamwe n’amashirahamwe yo mu gisata c’abigenga
 Blinken yavuze ati: “Hari ahantu harunze imiriyoni 20 z’amatoni y’ingano zazibiriwe mu bigega hafi ya Odesa, hamwe no mu mato yuzuye ingano azibiriwe ku kivuko ca Odesa kubera Uburusiya bwugaye imihora”
 Blinken yavuze nk’uko Charles Michel avuga, ko hari amakuru yo kwizera ko Uburusiya “buriko buranyaga urukombamazi” intete za Ukraine kugira ngo buzigurishe ku nyungu zabwo

