Gushika ku mutaga hagati imboneshakure (television) y’Uburusiya ntaco yari bwavuge ku c’uko iminsi 100 irumanye kuva Uburusiya buteye Ukraine
 Nyinshi mu mboneshakure zikurikirwa cane mu Burusiya zataganguye amakuru yazo yo um gitondo zagiriza Ukraine gutera ata gutoronya  ibisasu ku turere tutagenzurwa na reta
 Imboneshakure igenzurwa na Kremlin (ibiro vy’umukuru w’igihugu), Rossiya1, yavuze ko aba-nationalists bateye Mariupol na Donetsk’’ um gihe Channel One nayo, nayo nyene igenzurwa na reta, itanga uburorero bushasha bw’ubunyamwuga n’ukwitanga   vyerekanwa n’igisirikare c’Uburusiya um kugwanira Donbas’’
 Nta n’imwe ivuga ko ‘igikorwa ca gisirikare  kidasanzwe’ c’Uburusiya muri UKraine  conjiye um munsi waco ugira 100
 Imbere y’uko intambara itangura, abasigura uko ibintu biriko biragenda bari babwiye ababakurikira ko vyashoboka ko  bitwara  Uburusiya iminsi mike gusa kugira bwifatire Ukraine
 Ku wa kane, urubuga rwigenga Meduza rwanditse ko hari abarubwiye ko reta yari yategegetse ibinyamakuru kudacisha um kanwa ivy’uko  ivy’iminsi 100
 Rimwe mu masoko ya Meduza muri Kremlin ryayibwiye riti: ‘’ Guhagarara cane ku matariki ajanye bn’intambara bishobora gutuma abarusiya bibaza ivyari bigamijwe n’ico gitero n’ingene coba kimaze gushobora canke kunanirwa kubishikako
’’ Ibi bihushanye cane n’ibivugwa n’ibinyamakuru muri Ukraine aho imboneshakure iriko ikravuga ibiba uyu munsi ku civugo ‘Iminsi 100 yo kurya umutima amenyo’’
 Uwushikiriza amakuru ku mboneshakure yigenga Prymy TV yavuze ati: ‘’Uyu si umunsi wo kwigina kandi twizeye ko ata minsi 200 tuzokwibuka kuva intambara itanguye
 Amezi arenga atatu araheze kuva intambara itanguye
