Kugura no gutunga inkoho zose umuntu ashobora kugendana bishobora gucibwa burundu muri Canada, nk'uko vyavuzwe n'umushikiranganji wa mbere w'ico gihugu Justin Trudeau
 Reta yiwe yashikirije integuro y'itegeko rishasha ryohagarika  gutunga ku giti cawe inkoho zose ntonto
 Iryo tegeko ntiryoca rivanaho gutunga inkoho buno nyene - ariko rvyotuma kuzigura bitemerwa n'amategeko
 Integuro ya Tudeau ije mu gihe muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika  bahana urubibe umuntu afise inkoho aherutse kwiha inkumbi mw'ishure ry'intango ryo muri Texas aho yishe abantu 21
 Iyo nteguro yashikirijwe inama  nshingamateka ya Canada ku wa mbere, ituma bidashoka kugura, kugurisha, kurungika canke kwinjiza inkoho ahariho hose mu gihugu
 "Uretse ugukoresha inkoho mu nkino  no guhiga, nta yindi mpamvu n'imwe ihari  y'uko umuntu muri Canada akenera inkoho mu buzima bwa minsi yose," nk'uko Trudeau yabwiye abamenyeshamakuru
 "Mu gihe tubona ubukozi bw'ikibi buguma bwiyongera, n'inshingano zacu ko tubandanya kugira ico dukoze"
 Nirwo rugero rwa mbere rukomeye kurusha izindi reta  yiwe igerageje  mu nzira yo kubuza gutunga inkoho
 Iyo nteguro yosaba kandi ko agasaho k'amasasu kagabanywa ubunini kugira ntikazorenze amasasu atanu icarimwe
 Kandi abantu bose bazwi mu ntureka zo mu ngo canke  mu vyaha vyo kuburagiza abandi bakoresheje inkoho, boca bakwa impusha zo kuzitunga
 Bitandukanye no muri reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, gutunga inkoho muri Canada ntivyanditswe mw'ibwirizwa nshingiro , ariko ibigwanisho bicira  umuriro biragwiriye, na cane cane mu bice vyo hagati mu gihugu
 Canada isanganywe amategeko akaze ku bijanye no gutunga inkoho gusumba umubanyi wayo wo mu bumanuko kandi ku mwaka  hashika amasanganya make kurusha aturutse kuri ivyo bigwanisho
 Nk'akarorero, inkoho zose zitegerezwa kuba zugaranywe kandi zitarimwo amasasu kandi uwushaka kugura inkoho kahise kiwe  gategerezwa  gusuzumwa neza
 Ariko ubu bwa vuba  hari abagiye baratera akamo ko amategeko yo gutunga inkoho yokomezwa gusumba , na cane cane inyuma y'iraswa ryahitanye abantu
 Mu kwezi kwa kane mu 2020, umugabo afise inkoho yigize umuporisi yarishe abantu 22 muri Nova Scotia -kikaba arico gitigiri ca mbere kinini c'abantu bapfuye muri ubwo buryo muri kahise ka Canada
 Muri iyo minsi , Trudeau yaciye afata ingingo buno nyene yo kubuza gutunga  ubwoko butandukanye bw'ibigwanisho bushika  1
500
 Iryo tegeko ryoca rigumiza ku rugero rw'ubu  igitigiri c'ibigwanisho   bitunzwe mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko

Indinganizo nshasha yo gutanga impusha zo kwinjira mu Bwongereza (visa)  igamije gukwegakwega ''incabwenge za mbere'' zihejeje kaminuza hirya no hino kw'isi nta kaminuza n'imwe yo muri Afrika yashize ku rutonde rw'aho abafise izo mpapuro bashobora kuva
 Ibi vyatumye haba imyidogo ko incabwenge z'abanya-Afrika bakumiriwe - n'ubwo abanya-Afrika bize kuri kaminuza ziri kuri urwo rutonde bashobora gusaba
 Uwo ariwe wese yahejeje mu myaka itanu iheze kuri izo kaminuza ziza kw'isonga zitari izo mu Bwongereza yemerewe gusaba
 Abafise  urupapuro rw'umutsindo rwa kaminuza bafise amahiwe hatarabwe iyo bavukiye kandi ntibazokenera ko haba hari akazi kabonotse kugira basabe
 Ariko uburyo ingene urwo rutonde rw'izo kaminuza z'irya n'ino kw'isi rwakozwe vyatumye ata kaminuza n'imwe yo muri Afrika ijamwo
 Kugira umuntu ashobore gusaba, ategerezwa kuba yize muri kaminuza iri muri 50 ziza kw'isonga ku ntonde nibura zibiri mu zikorwa na Times Higher  Education World University Rankings, Quacquarelli Symonds World University Rankings, canke na  The Academic Ranking of World Universities z'umwaka aba yahejejemwo
 Kaminuza 37 nizo ziri kuri urwo rutonde - nyinshi muri zo ni izo muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ariko harimwo na zimwe zimwe z'i Buraya na Aziya
 "Ibirabwa mu gutora kaminuza zija kuri urwo rutonde biha amahirwe amakaminuza amaze imyaka amajana aronka uburyo bwinshi bwo gukora," ivyo  Amina Ahmed El-Imam wo kuri kaminuza ya Ilorin muri Nigeria yabibwiye   New Scientist magazine
 Ati: "Nk'umuntu ava muri Nigeria yaciye PhD (doctorat) mu Bwongereza, biravuna umutima kubona hakiri integuro zishirwaho zikumira abanya-Africa"
 "Iyo ndinganizo yoba isigura ko ata bantu ku giti cabo  bahejeje kaminuza zo muri Afrika bafise ubushobozi ku rugero rwo hejuru?"
Ku gihamana habonetse amatohoza yatoye uko uwahoze ari umukuru wa  Gambia  yakoresheje amafaranga y'inkomoko mbi mu kuyaguramwo inzu y'agaciro kanini muri  Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika
 Ubu noneho sentare yafashe ingingo ko iyo nzu y'agaciro ka miriyoni 3 z'amadorari (hafi miriyaridi 6 z'amafaranga y'Uburundi  canke miriyaridi 3 z'amafaranga y'Urwanda)  iri mu buraruko bw'intara ya Maryland, hafi y'umugwa mukuru Washington DC, itegerezwa gufatwa ikakwa uwo yanditsweko n'uwo  yahora ari  umutegetsi wa Gambia Yahya Jammeh
 Amafaranga azova mw'igurishwa ry'iyo nzu  azofasha abagiriwe "nabi n'ukurya ibiturire hamwe n'ugukoresha nabi ubutegetsi"  vyakozwe n'uwo yahoze atwara  igihugu, nk'uko bivugwa n'abategetsi  bo muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika
 Amatohoza y'igisata  c'ubutungane (department of justice, DOJ)  yatoye ko amafaranga yakoreshejwe mu kugura iyo nzu  y'ivyumba bitandatu yavuye mu biturire
 "Maryland si aho kunyegeza amafaranga y'abategetsi barya ibiturire  bayivye abanyagihugu babo," nk'uko bivugwa na  Selwyn Smith, umwe mu bantu bakurikirana ikibazo c'iyo nzu
 Ariko  amatohoza y'abaharanira uburenganzira niyo yabanje gushira ahabona ico kibazo, haraheze imyaka cumi
 Ubutegetsi bwa Jammeh bwamaze imyaka 22 hanyuma bukarangira mu 2017, bwamenyekanye cane mu kurangwa n'ibiturire kandi  bwaravuzweko cane ihonyangwa ry'agateka ka zina muntu harimwo kwica no gupfunga abamunegura
 Kuva ico gihe hagiye haramenyekana vyinshi biciye mu murwi wa Gambia wo kumenya ukuri, gusubiza hamwe no gushumbusha, muri iyi ndwi wasavye ko yokurikiranwa ku "vyaha injojo"
 Asanzwe amaze guhakana ko ata kabi yakoze
 Mu gihe c'ubutegetsi bwiwe, abanya-Gambia baharanira uburengenzira baba hanze bumvise ko boba ijwi ry'abadafise aho bavugira
 Sohna Sallah  yari umwe muri bo
 Mu 2010, ikinyamakuru c'abanya-Gambia gishingiye muri Amerika canditse ko umugore wa  Jammeh, Zineb, yaguze inzu muri karere k'abakire ka Potomac, nk'uko Sallah yabwiye BBC
 Ariko aho yari  itumbereye neza na neza ntihari hazwi
 "Twarihweje neza impapuro zerekeye  igurishwa ry'amazu muri ako karere hanyuma tubigwako," nk'uko uwo mugore w'imyaka 49 yavuze, aho akavuga ko abo babikoranye ari abo mu runani rwa  Union of Gambian Activists (Duga)
 Izina ry'umwe mu baguzi - the MYJ Family Trust - ryateye amakenga
 "Twibajije tuti: 'Hari umuntu ariko aragerageza kunyegeza ko baguze iyi nzu
'" Ikindi, Y na J vyahuriranye n'uko arizo ndome zitangura amazina ya prezida
 Kubera ataba kure y'aho, madame Sallah yaciye atangura kuja araca muri ako kabarabara ka Bentcross Drive kugira arabe ko ata muntu yohabona
 Yavuze n'agatwengo ari i muhira iwe muri  Bethesda hafi y'aho ati: "Twarakunda guca hafi y'aho hanyuma umunsi umwe dusanga umugore wiwe ariko ahagarika imodoka hanyuma turibaza tuti :"Ego, iyi ni ya nzu
'" Mu nyuma abo muri Duga, kubera bakeka ko amafaranga yo kugura iyo  nzu yari yavuye mu nzira ziteye kubiri n'amategeko, baciye batangaura kuja baragira imyiyerekano imbere y'iyo nzu
 Baciye babohera ibendera rya Gambia kw'irembo ry'iyo nzu baca bashinga imbere yayo urwandiko ruvuga ingo :"Iyi nzu iragurishwa, n'abanya-Gambia
" Baciye batangura kuja bararungikira ababanyi inzandiko zo kugerageza kubamenyesha  ivyo Jammeh yagirizwa gukora mu gihugu
 Aho bitwegereje, imwe mu mazu  yegereye aho yari iyo kwa Teodoro Obiang Nguema, amaze imyaka mirongo atwara igihugu ca Guinee Equatoriale , nk'uko ikinyamamuru Washington Post cavyanditse mu 2017
 Nawe yagirizwa ibiturire no guhonyanga uburenganzira bw'ikiremwa muntu, ivyo nawe ahakana
 Nta wuzi ko muri ako karere aho  atawukeneye kumenya ivyerekeye umubanyi, hari ico vyababwiye
 Ababa muri iyo nzu ya Jammeh vyarabashavuza,  rimwe na rimwe bagahamagara igiporisi, nk'uko bivugwa na Sallah
 Ariko ivy'uko iyo nzu yofatwa vy'ukuri vyagiye gutangura Jammeh amaze kuva ku butegetsi hanyuma akaja mu buhungiro muri Guinée Equatoriale inyuma yo gutsindwa amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu yo mu 2016
 Ubutegetsi bushasha bwa Gambia bwaciye bushiraho umurwi wo gutohoza  uko ibiturire vyari vyifashe  mu gihe c'ubutegetsi bwiwe
 Mu cegeranyo cawo co mu 2019, werekanye ko igihugu casahuwe vy'ikirenga
 Ibintu bitangaje birimwo nka pistolet (inkoho nto umuntu ashobora kugendana) z'inzahabu, ziri mu vyatowe muri imwe mu mazu ya Jammeh  muri Gambia, ariko igitigiri c'amazu yose yari  afise nico catangaje
 Uwo mugwi wasanze uwo yahoze ari umukuru w'igihugu yari afise amazu  281 mu gihugu, hamwe n'iyo yo muri Amerika n'iyindi yo muri Maroc, kandi akaba yari afise ama-konte ya banki arenga 100
 Nta kuntu iyo nzu yari kuba yarayiguze akoresheje amafaranga y'umushashara yahembwa, uwo mugwi uca usanga kandi yarigaruriye amafaranga arenga miriyoni 300 z'ama dorari
 Uwo mugwi wasanze kandi amafaranga angana na miriyoni imwe y'amadorari  yakatishirijwe kwa  Zineb Jammeh
 Menshi muri ayo mafaranga yari agenewe ibigo vy'ubugiraneza, harimwo na Operation Save the Children Foundation
 "Hafi  amafaranga yose y'iyo Fondation yononywe ku bintu ubiravye vyari bigamije  kwerekana neza izina rya Zineb Jammeh   hagufasha abana ba Gambia", nk'uko vyavuzwe n'icegerenyo c'uwo mugwi
 Vyatowe kandi ko Jammeh yaka amafaranga abantu kugira abahe impauro z'uburenganzira bwo kwihariza isoko ryo kwinjiza mu gihugu ibidandazwa bimwe bimwe birimwo ibitoro
 Kandi yaca akoresha iterabwoba ryo kubaka ubwo burenganzira kugira babadanye bamuha ayandi mafaranga
 Aho niho bivugwa ko havuye amafaranga yo kugura iyo nzu yo muri Pontomac
 Bafatiye ku gikorwa c'uwo mugwi, igisata c'ubutungane ca Amerika caciye gitanga ido n'ido ry'ingene vyagenze
 Mu kwezi kwa Mukakaro (7) mu 2010,  kompanyi y'ibitoro yabwiwe ko uburenganzira bwo kwihariza kwinjiza ibitoro bwari bugiye kurangira mu mpera z'uwo mwaka
 Nyene iyo kompanyi yaciye yegera Jammeh  kugira amusabe ko ubwo burenganzira bwo kwihariza iyo soko bwogumaho gushika mu 2014
 Haheze iminsi 11, umuriyoni w'amadorari waciye uva kuri konte y'iyo kompanyi yari muri banki ya Gambia Trust Bank Ltd,  uwo munsi nyene umukuru w'igihugu aca  yemerera iyo kompanyi kugumana uburenganzira bwo kwihariza isoko, nk'uko igisata c'ubutungane  kibivuga
 Umunsi ukurikira haciye huguruzwa konte muri iyo banki  kw'izina rya MYJ Family Trust
 Hanyuma umuriyoni w'amadorari uca urungikwa kuri iyo konte  mu bice bitatu n'umukozi w'iyo kompanyi
 Amaherezo ayo mafaranga yahavuye arungikwa kuri konte y'umuntu akora ibijanye n'amazu muri Amerika
 Mu minsi ikurikira, ayandi mafaranga angana na miriyoni 2,5 z'amadorari  yaciye arungikwa muri Amerika biciye muri banki  hanyuma ku wa 20 Nyakanga/Nzeri  iyo nzu yo muri Pontomac ica iragurwa miriyoni 3,5 z'amadorari
 
