Abakuru b'igihugu vy'Ubufaransa n'Ubudagi  basavye Perezida Vladimir Putin w'Uburusiya kuja mu biganiro "amaso mu yandi kandi ashimitse", n'umukuru w'igihugu ca Ukraine, nk'uko bivugwa n'ibiro vy'umukuru wa reta y'Ubudagi
 Emmanuel Macron, umukuru w'igihugu  c'Ubufaransa, hamwe na Olaf Scholz umukuru wa reta y'Ubudagi (Chancelier/Chancellor) bavuganye na Perezida Putin kuri terefone mu kiringo c'iminota 80
 Aba bategetsi babiri "bashimangiye ko ari ngombwa ko intambara ihagarara vuba bwango kandi ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zitahukanwa", nk'uko bivugwa n'ibiro vy'umukuru wa reta y'Ubudagi
 Nk'uko bivugwa na Kremlin (ibiro vy'umukuru w'igihugu c'Uburusiya), Perezida Putin yababwiye ko Moscou yiteguriye gusubira mu biganiro na Kyiv
 Ntivuga ariko ko ibiganiro amaso mu yandi bishoboka hagati ya Perezida Putin na mugenziwe wa Ukraine, Volodymyr Zelensky
 Imbere y'aha, Perezida Zelensky yari yavuze ko ata shaka afise ryo kuja mu biganiro, ariko akavuga ko ari vyo bishobora kuba inzira nyyo yo kurangira intambara
 Intumwa z'Uburusiya n'iza Ukraine ziramaze kubonana incuro zitari nke amaso mu yandi canke bari kure na kure  kuva Uburusiya butanguye igitero ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), ariko utu twigoro twahavuye duhagarara
 Ubufaransa n'Ubudagi kandi vyasavye Putin kurekura abarwanyi ba Ukraine 2500 bafashwe mpiri ku rugamba bakagirwa imbohe z'intambara kuri rwa ruganda rw'ivyuma rwa  Azovstal i Mariupol
 Uru ruganda runini rwabaye agace ka nyuma k'isekaniro muri ico gisagara kiri ku nkengera y'inyanja, camaze igihe cose gicucagirwa amabombe y'urutavanako n'ingabo z'Uburusiya ubu kikaba ari umusaka
 Mu ntango za kuno kwezi, abategetsi ba Moscou bavuze ko abarwanyi ba nyuma bariko barwanira uru ruganda bamanitse amaboko, mu gihe Perezida Zelensky avuga ko bahawe uruhusha rwo kuhava
 Uburusiya bwari bwavuze ko abarenga 900 muri abo barwanyi batwawe mw'ibohero ryuguruwe rya Olenivka, ikigwati kiri mu karere kari mu minwe y'Uburusiya muri Donesk
 Bakeya muri bo bakomeretse cane batwawe mu bitaro mu gisagara ca Novoazovsk, muri Donesk nyene
 Ukraine yizeye ko bazorekurwa mu mugambi wo guhanahana impfungwa - ariko Uburusiya ntiburavyemeza
 Bamwe mu bashingamateka bavuga ko aba barwanyi bakwiye kurengutswa mu bucamanza canke mbere bakanyongwa
 Muri ico kiganiro nyene, aba bategetasi b'Ubufaransa n'Ubudagi basavye kandi Putin kwugurura ikivuko ca Odesa muri Ukraine cugawe n'Uburusiya, kugira ngo intete zishobore gushorwa hanze
 Kremlin ivuga ko Perezida Putin yemeye ko agiye kuraba icokorwa, kugira ngo ntihahave haba ikibazo c'imfungurwa kw'isi - ariko akaba yasavye Uburengero ko bwokuraho ibihano bwafatiye igihugu ciwe
 Uburusiya kandi bwagabishije Ubufaransa n'Ubudagi ku ngendo yavyo yo kwongereza ibirwanisho biha Ukraine, akavuga ko bishobora gutuma indyane ziyongera kandi zikamara igihe kirekire
 Abategetsi ba Ukraina bavuga ko intambara zibandanya mu mabarabara y'igisagara ca Severodonetsk kiri mu buseruko, akarere ko hirya cane mu buseruko kakiri mu minwe ya Ukraine
 Buramatari w'intara ya Luhansk, Serhiy Haidai, avuga ko Abarusiya babandanya bacucagira amabombe ico gisagara, n'aho ingabo zabo zahatakarije ibitari bike
 Ku wa gatanu, abategetsi bavuze ko bibiri vya bitatu vyaco vyagoswe n'ingabo z'Uburusiya
 Buramatari Haidai yamenyesheje ko ingabo za Ukraine zashobora kuva muri Severodonetsk, mu kuvuga ati: "Birashoboka ko biba ngombwa ko bavayo kugira ngo ntibahave bugaranirwayo"
 Avugana na BBC ejo ku wa gatandatu, umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Ukraine, Denys Shmyhal yavuze ko igitero c'Uburusiya ku gihugu ciwe cabomoye ibirometero 25
000 vy'amabarabara, ibiraro bitari bike, hamwe n'ibibuga vy'indege 12
 Ibigo birenga 100 vy'amashure, amavuriro arenga 500, hamwe n'amahinguriro 200, navyo nyene vyaratikiye canke birononwa, nk'uko abivuga
 Asaba ko Uburusiya bwotegekwa kuriha ivyo "bwasambuye", akavuga ko amatungo y'Uburusiya yafashwe yorungikwa muri Ukraine kugira ngo akoreshwe mu bikorwa vyo gusanura igihugu

Umuserukizi w'Uburusiya mu Bwongereza yabwiye BBC ko atibaza ko igihugu ciwe kizohava gikoresha ibirwanisho ruhonyanganda mu ntambara na Ukraine
 Andrei Kelin avuga ko amategeko ya gisirikare y'Uburusiya atemera ko ibirwanisho nk'ibi  bikoreshwa mu ntambara nk'iyi ya Ukraine
 Avuga ko Uburusiya bufise amategeko akaze cane ajanye n'ikoreshwa ry'ibi birwanisho, cane cane mu gihe ukubaho kw'igihugu kugeramiwe
 Yabwiye ikiganiro Sunday Morning ati: "Ntaco bisa bisana n'igikorwa kibandanya"
 Igihe Vladimir Putin ahamagarira igisirikare kumera magabo zigategura ibirwanisho ruhonyanganda mu mpera z'ukwa kabiri, haciye imisi mike igitero gitanguye, isi yose yafashe ko yari agabishije ko yashobora kubikoresha
 Perezida Putin avuga ko ivyo yavuze vyavuye ku gasomborotso k'ibihugu vyo mu Burengero hamwe n'ishirahamwe OTAN ryo kwivunira umwansi hamwe rihurikiyemwo ivyo bihugu
 Ariko umushikiranganji w'Ubwongereza ajejwe kwivuna abansi Ben Wallace yavuze ko uko kwari ugushaka kuzimagiza abantu ku "biriko biragenda nabi muri Ukraine"
 Yavuga ko igitero c'Uburusiya kitariko kiragenda uko categuwe, kandi ko Putin yashaka no  "kwibutsa amakungu" ko Uburusiya bufise ibikoresho vyo kuzibira aboshaka kubutera
 Muri ico kiganiro yagiranye na  Clive Myrie wa BBC rimwe na rimwe akaza arishura ibidahuye, uyu aserukira Uburusiya yahakanye amakuru avuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya ziriko ziratera amabombe abasivire kandi ko ivyaha vy'intambara bwagirizwa mu gisagara ca Bucha ari "irementanya"
 Abajijwe ati "Kubera iki Uburusiya buriko bukora iyi ntambara nk'uku, bukora ivyaha vyo mu ntambara?",  Kelin yishuye ati: "Umukuru w'igisagara ca Bucha mw'itangazo ryiwe aremeza ko ingabo z'Uburusiya yagiye, vyose bimeze neza kandi haratekanye, igisagara kiri mu buzima busanzwe
 "Nta na kimwe kiriko kiraba, nta biziga biri ku mabarabara
 Ariko hanyuma, vyose bimaze gukorwa - ariko


" Ariko rero Myrie yahavuye amusatira : "None nyakwubahwa, ibi vyose ni irementanya? Vyose ni irementanya gusa? Ibi vyemezo vyose ni irementanya?" Uyu muserukizi yaciye yishura ati: "Twebwe tubona ko ari irementanya
 Rikoreshwa mu gutoba ibiganiro"
 Uburusiya bwarigeze kuvuga ibi imbere y'aha, aho umushikiranganji w'imigenderanire Sergei Lavrov yavuze ko amashusho y'ibiziga i Bucha vyari "irementanya" , igihe ingabo z'Uburusiya ziviriyeyo
 Aya majambo yarabeshujwe n'abatari bake bavyiboneye babwiye BBC ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zabiciye ababo
 Avuga ku mukwe wiwe, umugabo umwe yavuze ati: "Yari umugabo w'umunyamahoro, se rugo, yari abeshejweho n'ugusudira, yari afise ingorane z'uruti rw'umugongo kandi yari yaramugaye ubuzima bwiwe bwose"
 Amasanamu y'ibigendajuru nayo nyene asa n'ayabeshuza ibivugwa na Moscou, akerekana ibiziga birambaraye mw'ibarabara hasigaye indwi zibiri ngo Abarusiya bave muri ico gisagara

Igisirikare c'Urwanda (RDF) gisaba igisirikare ca Repubulika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo (FARDC) kurekura abasirikare baco baherutse gufatwa mpiri, nk'uko biri mw'itangazo rigufi ryaraye risohowe na RDF
 Ni nyuma y'aho abakoresha imbuga hwaniro  bahanahaniye amasanamu y'abasirikare babiri b'Urwanda bavugwa ko bafatiwe muri Congo bariko barwana ku ruhande rw'umuhari  w'inyeshamba M23 uhanganye n'igisirikare ca DR Congo
 Reta y'Urwanda yoyo ivuga ko  aba basirikare banyurujwe "inyuma y'agasomborotso" k'igisirikare ca Congo ku wa mbere w'iyi ndwi, aho "vya muzinga bitari bike vyatewe ku butaka bw'u Rwanda"
 Mw'iri tangazo, RDF ivuga ko aba basirikare bayo bafashwe bari mu bikorwa vyo gucungera umutekano inyuma ya vya muzinga vyarashwe ku butaka bw'u Rwanda ku wa 23 Rusama (5)
 Rivuga riti: "FARDC hamwe na FDLR bakoze igitero kuri RDF ku mupaka wacu, kandi abasirikare babiri b'ingabo z'u Rwanda baranyurujwe igihe bari mu bikorwa vyo gucungera umutekano"
 Aba basirikare bazwi ku mazina ya Cpl Nkundabagenzi Elysee and Pte Ntwari Gad
 Rirangiza rivuga riti: "Turasavye abategetsi ba Repubulika y'intwaro Rusangi ya Congo bakorana cane n'imirwi y'inyeshamba yakoze jenoside gukora kugira ngo abasirikare ba RDF barekurwe"
 Reta ya Congo iherutse kwagiriza Urwanda ko rufasha umuhari M23 watangajwe ko ari uw'iterabwoba, ivyo Urwanda Ruhakana, ahubwo, nk'uko vyasubiriye kugaragarira muri uru rwandiko, rukagiriza Congo ko ikorana n'umuhari FDLR wagirizwa ko wakoze ihonyabwoko ryo mu Rwanda mu 1994
 Reta ya congo yoyo ivuga ko ibi yagirizwa n'Urwanda ari ivyitwazo kugira ngo ishigikire M23
 Ntaco igisirikare ca Congo kiratangaza ku bisabwa n'igisirikare c'Urwanda kuri aba basirikare babiri bafashwe bakaba bari mu minwe ya FARDC

Umwaka wiza cane wa Liverpool yari yitezemwo umunezero w'ibikombe bine  waraye urangiye mu marira inyuma y'imidugararo yabereye i Paris imbere y'urukino
 Ijoro ryakeye ryabaye akamuna kuri Liverpool n'abafana bayo ku ngero zose umuntu yokwiyumvira mu gihe Real Madrid yoyo yakoze ivyo yama ikora hanyuma iterura igikombe ca Ligue des Champions/Champions League, ku ncuro igira 14
 Intsinzi ya Real y'igitsindo kimwe cinjijwe na  Vinicius Junior ku munota wa 59, yandikishije izina ry'umumenyereza  Carlo Ancelotti mu gitabo ntibagiranwa c'amateka atahukanye igikombe kigira kane nk'umumenyereza muri rino higanwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere iwabo (Champions League)
 Kuri Liverpool uyu musi mubi kuri bo wugaye imisi itandatu y'amarira inyuma y'aho itakarije ihiganwa ry'Ubwongereza Premier League aho ku musi wa nyuma  Manchester City ariyo yahavuye igitahukana, isumbije Liverpool inota rimwe ritarenga ntirirenguke, hanyuma ikaba yaraye itakaje imbere y'uyu murwi w'igihangange kandi ufise uburambe, Real Madrid
 Ariko, uru rukino rwa nyuma rwaraye rukinywe ntiruzokwibukirwa ku gutsindwa kwa Liverpool n'intsinzi ya Real gusa
 Ruzokwibukwa kandi ku midugararo yabereye hanze y'ikibuga Stade de France mu masaha makeya imbere y'uko rutangura, aho ibarabara rigana mu nzira yo mu kuzimu hapande y'ikibuga ryuzuye isinzi ry'abafana ba Liverpool  mu buryo buteye ubwoba
 Wegereye aba bafana, warashobora kwumva ingene bari bashushe mbere uko iminota yagenda niko uburakari bwagenda bwiyongera mu gihe batashobora kuva aho bari kubera ubwinshi bwabo
 Vyari ibintu bitaryoheye ijisho
 Mu gihe icuka kibi cagenda kiduga, n'imirongo miremire yagenda yiyongera ku miryango y'ikibuga, vyagiye kurangira igipolisi c'Ubufaransa gikoresheje ivyuka vy'ipiripiri na vya vyuka vyokera kugira birukane abafana, biba ngombwa ko urukino rutangura rucerewe iminota 36 yose mu gihe uruhande rw'ikibuga rwari rwateguriye Liverpool rwagumye rufise abantu bake cane
 Liverpool yasavye ko haba amatohoza ku vyabaye mu gihe UEFA ivuga ko inzitiro "zazibiwe n'ibihumbi vy'abafana bari baguze amatike y'amanyanga ataco yabafashije"
 Iki nico cuka caranze uru rukino aho Liverpool yagerageje incuro nyinshi kurondera igitsindo ariko ikiseka ku munyegori yari yahumaganye, Umubirigi Thibaut Courtois
 Mu gihe abakinyi ba Liverpool bari baguye bukwi mu kibuga, Trent Alexander-Arnold wewe yamaze iminota itari mike yajumarariwe, atabona iyo aja n'iyo ava
 Jurgen Klopp n'abahungu biwe ntibazokwibagira uyu mwaka w'inkino berekaniyemwo ubuhinga n'inguvu zidasanzwe mu gutsindira ibikombe bibiri ariko ukaza kurangira mu mubabaro
 Alexander-Arnold yaboneka ko yari yacitse intege bidasanzwe, atari gusa umubabaro wo gutsindwa,  ahubwo ku kungene Vinicius yamuciye inyuma akamutsindana igitsindo cagiye kuvamwo intsinzi ya Real
 Ariko rero hariho ibintu vyo kwihweza neza, cane cane ku murwi nk'uyu w'igihangange kandi uzwi ko usatira bikomeye
 Liverpool yatahukanye ibikombe Carabao Cup na FA Cup, vyompi kuri ya mipira itererwa ku metero 11 (penalties) itsinze Chelsea
  Ibi bisigura ko mu nkino zitatu za nyuma zose (finales) Liverpool itashoboye gutsinda igitsindo na kimwe mu kiringo c'urukino, harimwo mbere no mu biringo bibiri vy'inyongera (prolongations/extra-time)
 Mu gihe uyu murwi ufise abasatirizi badasanzwe nka Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane, Luis Diaz, Roberto Firmino na Diogo Jota, ntivyumvikana na gato ukungene badashobora gutera ibitsindo
 Muri Carabao Cup na FA Cup nta ngaruka vyagize, ariko nijoro vyaragize ingaruka
 Hanyuma uwatumye ibi vyose ni Courtois yari yambaye urwaga, mu gukurayo imipira itandatu yose ya Salah wenyene, hamwe n'uwundi ukomeye watewe na Mane  akawuzibira hanyuma useka ku cuma c'igori imbere yo kwisanga hanze
 Ijoro ryakeye ryari nk'ukwihora kuri Salah inyuma y'ivyabaye mu 2018 mu rukino rwa nyuma nyene  aho asekaniye na Sergio Ramos bikaba ngombwa ko ava mu kibuga, akorora amosozi y'umubabaro inyuma y'iminota 30 gusa, urukino rukaba rwagiye kurangira Real ikubise Liverpool 3-1 i Kyiv muri Ukraine
 Salah azokwama yibaza igihe cose ingene vyanse ko yinjiza igitsindo na kimwe hano
 Ashobora kumara amajoro atari make mu ndoto mbi aho azokwama abona Courtois, uyu muntu umwe yamubereye ifuro ry'igiti
 Muri zino ndwi za nyuma, Liverpool yaboneka ko isa n'iyishaka gucika intege kubera ingene bitanga bidasanzwe ariko bikanka ko batsinda, kandi vyaraboneka mu minota ya nyuma uravye ingene bita kugira ngo bisubize iteka, ariko bikaba ivy'ubusa imbere y'uyu murwi w'igihangange wiganje muri iri higanwa rya Champions League, uzi kandi n'ingene ukenyura uwo bahanganye
 Muri uno mwaka urangiye, Klopp n'abahungu biwe ntaco batakoze, mbere kuri uyu wa Mungu bakaba biteze kwerekana ibikombe vyabo vya Carabao Cup na FA Cup mu mabarabara ya Liverpool, ariko wibaze ingene vyari kugenda iyo baramuka bateruye iki gikombe ca Champions League ku ncuro igira indwi
 Nta muntu n'umwe yiyumvira ko Liverpool yari kurangiza uyu mwaka w'inkino mu mubabaro uravye ingene basugereje Manchester City, muri Premier League gushika ku musi wa nyuma
 Uyu murwi wa Pep Guardiola wavuye iyo rwotera izuba ku musi wa nyuma w'ihiganwa kuko wabanje guterwa bibiri vyose ku busa na Aston Villa, imbere y'uko bivyukiranya bagatsinda bitatu mu minota itarenga itanu, gutyo babona kwigizayo Klopp n'abiwe
 Ariko mu rukino rwa nijoro, iyo ataba ubuhinga budasanzwe bwa Coutrois, iki gikombe ubu kiva kivugira i  Merseyside
 Nta nkeka ko Real yaciye mu nzira zitoroshe, kandi nk'umurwi washoboye gutsinda Paris St-Germain, Chelsea, Manchester City na Liverpool, koko urakwiye iki gikombe ca Champions League
 Aha nta keka
 Kuri Liverpool kumbure nta muntu yovuga ko uyu mwaka wabaye mubi - kuko bawumaze berekana ubuhinga bwo ku rwego rwo hejuru  - ariko akari ukuri karavugwa, urangiriye i Paris mu buryo budashimishije, mu mubabaro

Ivyizigiro vya Liverpool vyo gutsindira igikombe kigira indwi co mw'ihiganwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere I Bulaya (Champions League) birangiye mu mubabaro aho iguye mu minwe ya Real Madrid i Paris
 Umusatirizi wa  Brezili Vinicius Jr, niwe ayihumiye, mu kwinjiza igitsindo kimwe rudende mu rukino rwose, aho yari yiketswe ko yoba yari yaraririye, Trent Alexander-Arnold akaba ari we yatumye ahagarara neza, bituma Real Madrid itahukana iki gikombe kigize 14, aho nyene niyo iherutse gutsindira ihiganwa rya Espagne, La Liga
 Liverpool yaronse amahirwe menshi yo gutsinda ariko umunyegori Thibaut Courtois  yari yariye amavubi, uyu yahoze asamira Chelsea akaba yabanje gukurayo umupira wari utewe na Sadio Mane, imbere yo gukurayo uwundi mupira ukomeye wari utewe mw'igori na Mohamed Salah
 Mohamed Salah, yateshejwe iki gitsindo mu gihe yarondera kwihora ivyo yabonye mu rukino nk'uru nyene rwo mu 2018 na Real Madrid nyene, aho vyabaye ngombwa ko ava mu kibuga mu gice ca mbere kubera imvune
 Uru rukino rwategerezwa gutangura isaha imwe z'ijoro mu masaha mpuzamakungu (ni ukuvuga isaha zitatu z'ijoro mu masaha y'Uburundi n'Urwanda)  rwatanguye rucerewe iminota 36 yose, kubera "ibibazo vy'umutekano" inyuma y'aho hari amasanamu asohote yerekana isinzi ry'abantu hanze y'ikibuga bariko bagerageza kwinjira mu kibuga ca Stade de France
 Gutsindwa kwa Liverpool gutumye uyu murwi warondera gukora ibidasanzwe mu mupira w'amaguru mu gutahukana ibikombe bine muri uno mwaka w'inkino urangiye, utahira bibiri gusa, ica FA (FA Cup) hamwe n'ica Carabao (Carabao Cup)

Ingabo za Ukraine zirashobora kuva mu gisagara kinini co mu buseruko, Severodonetsk, mu gihe  ingabo z'Uburusiya ziri hafi kukigota, nk'uko bivugwa n'umutegtsi
 Serhiy Haidai, buramatari wa Luhansk, avuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya ziri mu gice kimwe c'iki gisagara
 "Birashobora ko, kugira ngo ntibahave bugaranwa, ari ngombwa ko bavayo"
 Kwigarurira akarere kose ka Donbas nico cabaye intumbero nyamukuru y'iyi ntambara ku Burusiya 
 Ukraine iriko iratabaza isaba ibirwanisho birasa kure kugira ngo ishobore guhangana n'Uburusiya bubandanya busatira, ariko gushika ubu Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ntizirashobora kuyibiha
 Ejo ku wa gatanu, umushikiranganji wa mbere w'Ubwongereza Boris Johnson yavuze ko Ukraine ikeneye ibirwanisho birasa kure kandi bitera ibisasu vyinshi ica rimwe
 Yabwiye ikinyamakuru Bloomberg ati: "Mfise ubwoba ko Putin, ku giciro kinini kuri we no ku gisirikare c'Uburusiya, abandanya atema atongora i Donbas"
 "Kumbure afise kuba ata kintu kiboneka arashikako, ariko abandanya atera intambwe buke buke, rero ni ngombwa ko tubandanya dufasha igisirikare ca Ukraine"
 I Severodonetsk, Haidai avuga ko inzu zirenga igice zasenyuwe kandi ko inyubakwa hafi zose zononywe, abayagihugu basigayeyo bari mu kangaratete
 Ibarabara riva muri ico gisagara rija hagati muri Ukraine riracari mu masasu y'urutavanako, ariko rirarengana, nk'uko abivuga
 Hanyuma kandi, ingabo zishigikiwe n'Uburusiya zarigaruriye igisagara ca Lyman kiri mu burengero bwa Severodonetsk, ibi bikazishoboza guca zibandanya gushika mu bisagara bikuru bikuru vya Slovyansk na  Kramatorsk
 N'umunyamakuru  Paul Kirby Gufata Lyman ni ikintu gikomeye ku ngabo zishigikiwe n'Uburusiya zigenda zisatira bukebuke mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 Urugamba rwo kurwanira iki gisagara ntirwari rworoshe, n'aho ingabo za Ukraine zari zatanguye gukura meza mu ntango z'ino ndwi
 Ni iyindi ntzinsi ikomeye ku Burusiya muri ino ndwi, inyuma y'aho bufatiye Svitlodarsk mu bumanuko
 Lyman ubwayo si igisagara kinini, ariko giha akaryo ingabo zishigikiwe n'Uburusiya kugenura ibarabara rikomeye riva mu buseruko rija mu burengero
 Bisigura kandi ko ubu zigeze ku birometero 20 uvuye mu gisagara ca Slovyansk, utera uja mu bumanuko bushira uburengero
 Izindi ntambara zikomeye ziri kure mu buseruko, aho ingabo z'Uburusiya zisugereje ibisagara bibiri vya  Severodonetsk na Lysychansk
 Ibi ni ibisagara bikomeye muri aka karere-mutima k'amahinguriro ka Ukraine kazwi nka Donbas, kugatakaza rukaba rwoba ari uruhombo rukomeye ku gisirikare
 Hanze y'urubuga rw'intambara, Perezida Vladimir Putin w'Uburusiya yagirije Ukraine "gutoba" umugambi w'amahoro mu kiganiro yagiranye kuri terefone n'umukuru wa reta (Chancelier/Chansellor)  ya Autriche/Austria Karl Nehammer
 Mu mpapuro zasohowe na Moscou zerekana ivyo bavuganye muri ico kiganiro, Putin arahakana ivyo igihugu ciwe cagirizwa ko ari co gituma imfungurwa zikena kw'isi kubera cazibiye ibivuko vya Ukraine, akavuga ko ahubwo ubu bukene buva ku bihano Amerika n'Ubumwe bwa Bulaya vyafatiye Uburusiya
 Ishirahamwe ONU riragabisha ko igitero c'Uburusiya gishobora guteza ikibazo c'imfungurwa kw'isi gishobora kumara imyaka myinshi
 Caratumye intete zishorwa hanze, nk'ibigori n'ingano, co kimwe n'amavuta yo guteka bigabanuka, ivyatumye n'ibiciro vy'ibifungurwa vyo kubisubiriza biduga cane
 Ibiciro vy'ibifungurwa ku rwego rw'isi vyaduze hafi kugera ku rugero rwababa 30% ibegeranije n'igihe nk'iki co mu mwaka uheze, nk'uko bivugwa na ONU
 Hagati aho, ishami ry'Ishengero rya Orthodox rya Ukraine i Moscou rivuga ko rihagaritse ubucuti n'Uburusiya kubera Ishengero rya Orthodox ry'Uburusiya rishigikiye iyi ntambara
 Mw'itangazo iri shengero ryasohoye, rivuga riti: "Turahakanye aho Kirill, umukuru w'ishengero i Moscou, [ Patriarch Kirill of Moscow] ahagaze


 kuri iyi ntambara"
 Ukraine ifise ikibanza kidasanzwe mw'Ishengero rya Orthodox ry'Uburusiya kandi ifise inyubakwa zikomeye
 Igice kimwe c'ishengero rya Orthodox rya Ukraine ryari ryamaze guhagarika ubucuti na Moscou mu 2019

Uwahoze ari umukuru w'igihugu wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Donald Trump atera akamo abashingamateka b'iki gihugu kwitaho gushira amafaranga mu mutekano w'amashure hakurungika imfashanyo ya gisirikare muri Ukraine
 Mw'ijambo yashikirije mu nama ihuza abashigikiye itegeko riha uburenganzira abanyagihugu gutunga inkoho, Trump ntabona ukungene Amerika "ishobora kuba ifise imiriyaridi 40 z'amadorari yo kurungikira Ukraine" ariko ikaba idashobora gukingira umutekano w'amashure
 Inama y'ishirahamwe ryishinze gukingira itegeko riha uburenganzira abanyagihugu gutunga inkoho, National Rifle Association (NRA), iriko ibera i Houston
 Avuze aya majambo inyuma y'imisi mike abantu 21, harimwo abana 19, biciwe mu gitero c'umusore yitwaje inkoho kw'ishure rimwe ryo muri Texas
 Mw'iri jambo yashikirije nijoro ku wa gatanu agakomerwa amashi menshi cane, Trump avuga ati: "Imbere y'uko tuza kwubaka ibindi bihugu kw'isi, twategerezwa kubanza kwubakira abana bacu amashure atekanye mu gihugu cacu"
 Mu ntango z'uku kwezi, inama nshingamateka na nkenguzamateka za Amerika  (Congrès/Congress) zaremeje ku rugero runini imfashanyo ya gisirikare kuri Ukraine ingana hafi n'imiriyaridi 40 z'amadorari y'abanyamerika
 Yose hamwe, abashingamateka n'abakenguzamateka bamaze kurungika imiriyaridi 54 z'amadorari y'abanyamerika muri Ukraine kuva Uburusiya buteye iki gihugu mu kwa kabiri
 Trump abandanya ati: "Congrès yategerezwa kwemeza vuba bwango kugarukana ifaranga ryose turakoreshejwe muri ya mafaranga yo gufasha abakozweko na Covid
 "Intara ni ziyasubize hanyuma akoreshwe ningoga mu gushiraho uburyo butavogerwa bwo gucungera umutekano ku mashure yose yo ku butaka bwacu"
 Trump ariyamiriza abasaba ko hoba ugucungera ibijanye no gutunga inkoho, akavuga ko abanyamerika bategerezwa kugira uburenganzira bwo kwivuna "akabi"
 Ahubwo asaba ko hosubirwamwo "kuva hasi gushika hejuru" integuro ijanye no gucungera umutekano w'amashure, nko gushinga irembo rimwe ricungerewe cane ku bigo vy'amashure, harimwo ubuhinga bwo gucungera ko ata muntu yinjiza icuma kandi ishure ryose rikaba rifise n'imiburiburi umupolisi yohabwa ikirwanisho
 Yagiriza aba Democrats kuzibira ingingo zo gucungera umutekano nk'izi
 Uyu mu Repubulika yahoze arongoye Amerika yatanguye ijambo ryiwe asoma amazina y'abaguye mu gitero c'umusore yitwaje inkoho i Uvalde, rimwe rimwe ryose rigakurikirwa n'inkengeri
 Ahejeje gusoma amazina y'abantu 21 bose biciwe muri ico gitero kw'ishure i Uvalde, Trump yavuze ati: "Kubera hari ikibi, ni kimwe mu bituma vyiza cane bituma itegeko rirekurira banyagihugu gutunga ikirwanisho, ntiribaka ikirwanisho"
 Iyi nama ya NRA - rifise abanywanyi imiriyoni zitanu -  yama iba uko umwaka utashe, iriko ibera ku birometero 450 uvuye i Uvalde, ahabereye iki gitero c'agahomerabunwa
 Imbere y'uko iyi nama itangura, abatari bake mu bashikirije ijambo bo ku ruhande rw'aba Conservateurs/Conservative hamwe n'abanyamuziki batangaje ko biyonjoroye - harimwo buramatari wa Texas  Greg Abbott, umukenguzamateka John Cornyn hamwe n'uwahinguye irya nkoho yakoreshejwe mu gitero ca Uvalde
 Trump yifatiye mu gahanga abo biyonjoroye, mu kubwira abari aho ati: "Jewe sinabahemukiye ngo ndeke kwitaba nk'abo bandi"
 Mw'iryo jambo ryiwe, Trump kandi yateye akamo Amerika "guhindura cane integuro ijanye n'abafise ibibazo vyo mu mutwe"
 Yarateye akamo nk'ako igihe yari akiri umukuru w'igihugu, n'aho muri ico gihe abamunegura bamwagirije ko yariko agerageza guhagarika amafaranga yari agenewe imigambi y'ubuvuzi harimwo no kwitaho abafise ibibazo vyo mu mutwe
 imbere y'uko Turmp ashikiriza ijambo, umukenguzamateka wo muri Texas Ted Cruz yavuze ko ibitero vy'abarasa abantu mu kivunga biva kuri ba serugo batitaho imiryango, abantu batakija mu masengero, imbuga hwaniro hamwe n'amavidewo y'udukino
 Umukenguzamateka Cruz ashimangira ko ashigikiye cane iri tegeko riha uburenganzira abanyagihugu gutunga inkoho, aca asaba abari bitavye iyi nama "ko mu kwishura ikibi batoca bahonyanga ibwirizwashingiro canke uburenganzira bw'abanyagihugu bagendera ku mategeko"
 Hanze y'aho iyo nama ibera, habaye imyiyerekano yahuriyemwo amajana n'amajana y'abatera ivyatsi ishiramawe NRA
 Bari bafise ivyapa vyanditseko ngo "NRA yica inzoya",  "kingira abana hagukingira inkoho", bafise n'imisaraba hamwe n'amasanamu y'abaguye muri ico gitero

Inama nkuru yo kwivuna abansi muri Repubulika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo itangaza ko kuva ubu umuhari M23 urwanya reta ari umuhari w'iterabwoba
 Mw'itangazo ryasomwe na Patrick Muyaya, umushikiranganji wa Congo ajejwe kumenyesha amakuru, yavuze ko iyo nama yagiriza igisirikare c'Urwanda ko gifashe mu mugongo uyu muhari
 Ati: "Amakuru atangwa n'abasirikare bari ku rubuga, amasanamu afiswe n'ingabo zacu, hamwe n'ivyemezo bitangwa n'abanyagihugu bacu, birerekana ata nkeka ko M23 ishigikiwe n'igisirikare c'Urwanda"
 Mu ngingo zindi zafashwe, ni uko ikompanyi y'indege ya leta y'Urwanda, Rwandair, yahagaritswe gusubira kwinjira muri Repubulika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo
 Reta y'Urwanda ntaco iravuga kuri ibi biri muri iri tangazo ry'inama nkuru y'ukwivuna abansi ya Congo, ariko umuvugizi wayo Alain Mukuralinda kuwa gatanu yabwiye BBC ko ata ruhara u Rwanda rufise mu bibera muri Congo
 Sibwo bwa mbere kandi RD Congo yagirije Urwanda gufasha umuhari M23, kandi si ubwa mbere u Rwanda rubihakanye
 Iyo nama ya Congo iragabisha Urwanda, ikarwagiriza ko ingendo  yarwo ari iyo gutoba utwigoro two kugarukana amahoro  biciye mu biganiro biriko bibera i Nairobi muri Kenya
 Iryo tangazo rivuga kandi riti: "Inama nkuru yo kwivuna abansi iriyamiriza yivuye inyuma umugambi w'ububeshi bukwiragizwa n'Urwanda, aho rwagiriza igisirikare ca Congo ko cifatanya n'imirwi y'inkorabara nk'urwitwazo mu gushigikira umurwi w'iterabwoba wa M23"
 Iyo nama ishimira kandi "Ubumwe bwa Afrika, Ishirahamwe mpuzamakungu ONU, Ubumwe bwa Bulaya, Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ububirigi n'ibindi, vyiyamirije iyindi ngendo igayitse ya M23 n'abavyeyi bayo"
 Umushikiranganji Muyaya atera akamo abanyagihugu "kwirinda kugwa mu mutego w'umwansi" bakabandanya bafatanye mu nda, kandi bakaguma barikanuye
 Iyo nama kandi yafashe ingingo yo gutumako uwuserukira Urwanda i Kinshasa kugira ngo bamumenyeshe akababaro ka Repubulika y'Intwaro Rusangi ya Congo
 Umviriza ingene Alain Mukuralinda yabwiye Prudent Nsengiyumva wa BBC Gahuzamiryango;
Umugore wo muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yariko yirenganira yarashe yica umugabo yariko ararasa umurwi w'abantu bari mu birori i Charleston muri Virginia y'uburengero
 Dennis Butler, umugabo w'imyaka 37 kandi azwi mu bukozi bw'ikibi, yarashwe igihe yariko arasa umurwi w'abantu 40 bari bibereye mu birori vyo guhimbaza umusi mukuru w'amavuko
 Umuvugizi w'igipolisi Tony Hazelett yavuze ko ububangutsi bw'uyu mugore bwarokoye ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kandi anaburizamwo uyu mugabo yariko arasa abantu mu kivunga
 Ibi bibaye mu gihe ik igihugu kiri mu mpari ku bijanye no gutunga inkoho inyuma y'igitero c'umusore yitwaje inkoho kw'ishure ryo muri Texas
 Butler yariko agendesha imodoka ku wa gatatu mu mugoroba igihe asabwa kugabanya umurindi kubera abana bariko barakina
 Mu nyuma yagiye kugaruka afise inkoho yo mu bwoko bwa AR-15 aca arasa abantu bari mu birori vy'amavuko hampande y'umuhana muri ico gisagara
 Hazelett yabwiye abanyamakuru ko uyo mugore yatabaye atigeze aba mu nzego zijejwe umutekano
 Ntiyatanze umwidondoro wiwe
 "Ni umunyagihugu asanzwe yari yitwaje inkoho atunze biciye mu mategeko
 Hanyuma hakwiruka ahunga, yahisemwo ahubwo guhangana n'iyo nkozi y'ikibi maze arokora ubuzima bw'abantu"
 Uyo mugore yagumye aho ivyo vyabereye, kandi ariko akorana neza n'abajejwe amatohoza
 Igipolisi kivuga ko uyo mugore atavyaha azokwagirizwa
 Kivuga kandi ko Butler yagiye gutorwa ari ikiziga afise n'ibikomere vy'amasasu menshi yarashwe
 Hazelett avuga ko bitaramenyekana neza ingene Butler yaronse ico kirwanisho, yari atunze kandi amategeko atabimurekurira kubera ivyaha vy'ubukozi bw'ikibi vyamwagiriye
 Aka kabi kabaye inyuma y'aho umusore yari afise inkoho arasiye akica abantu 21  kw'ishure ry'intango ryo muri Texas akoresheje inkoho yo mu bwoko bwa  AR-15, inkoho yaguze biciye mu mategeko
 Iki gitero catumye hasubira kuvyuka impari ku burenganzira bw'abantu ku giti cabo bwo gutunga inkoho, busanzwe butangwa n'ibwirizwashingiro rya Amerika

Umuvugizi wungirije wa leta y'u Rwanda Alain Mukuralinda avuga ko ata ruhara u Rwanda rufise mu mirwano hagati y'ingabo za DR Congo n'umutwe wa M23

Icegera c'umukuru wa Kenya William Ruto yasavye imbabazi umukuru w'igihugu  Uhuru Kenyatta batabandanije gucana uwaka inyuma y'amatora yo mu 2018
 Kuba  Ruto na Kenyatta batacumvikana vyageze ahantu bija ku mugaragraro
 Umukuru w'igihugu ntashigikiye Ruto mu kwitoza ngo amusubirire mu matora azoba mu kwezi kwa Myandagaro (8), ahubwo yahisemwo gushigikira uwutavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi Raila Odinga
 Ruto ivyo yabivuze mw'ikoraniro ry'igisabisho ngarukamwaka  categuwe n'inama nshingamateka - prezida Kenyatta akaba yari yacitavye
 Icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu yavugiye imbere y'abari aho, asaba abanya-Kenya ikigongwe ku ho reta itakoze neza - hanyuma  yita Kenyatta ''umugenzi wiwe mwiza''
 Yavuze ati: ''Ndazi kandi ko mu mabanga y'icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu nshobora kuba hari aho ntashitse ku vyo nari nitezweko n'umukuru wanje, nyakwubahwa umukuru w'igihugu - umugenzi wanje mwiza, ndagusavye imbabazi"
 Yabandanije  yifuriza ikiruhuko ciza umukuru w'igihugu
 Prezida Kenyatta ararangiza  uyu mwaka ikiringo ciwe ca kabiri ari naco ca nyuma
 Muri Kenya umukuru w'igihugu ntafise ububasha bwo gukura icegera ciwe - ashobora kuvanwaho gusa n'inama nshingamateka canke izindi nzira z'amategeko
 Raba video y'amajambo yashikirijwe na William Ruto
 BBC ntibazwa ibivuye ku zindi mbuga

Igisirikare ca Ukraine kirageramiwe gusumba ibindi bihe vyose kuva igitero c'Uburusiya gitanguye
 Ishobora kuba intambara bariko baratsindwa muri Luhansk, igice kimwe kiri mu buraruko bw'akarere ka Donbas
 Ibiro bikuru vy'igisirikare ca Ukraine bivuga ko Uburusiya busa n'uburiko buregeranya inguvu zabwo mu ntumbero yo gusubira gusatira
 Uburusiya bwongereje ibitero vyabwo ku rubuga rw'intambara muri Donbas yose  - bukaba buri hafi yo kurangiza igota rya  Severodonetsk, igisagara cari gitunze abantu 80
000 imbere y'intambara
 Abanya-Ukraine, nk'uko bisanzwe barwana nk'abita
 Izindi ngabo zibandanya zirungikwa gushigikira iziri muri urwo rugamba
 Mu minota mikeya, nagiye mbona ibimodoka vy'intambara 20, birimwo abasirikare, batera baja ku rugamba - biri kumwe n'ibimodoka ntamenwa hamwe n'ibindi bitera vya muzinga
 Ingabo za Ukraine zaragabanije umurindi w'Abarusiya ariko ntizababujije kubandanya basatira
 Ukraine iriko iratakaza abantu benshi
 Isoko ryo mu gisirikare muri Brigade ya 57 yambwiye ko umwe mu mirwi yabo wagiye ufise abantu 240 ukaba wagarutse usigaranye 140 gusa - abandi basigaye bishwe, bakomeretse canke bafashwe mpiri
 Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko Abarusiya bashobora kuba bariko bica ingabo za Ukraine 100 ku musi muri Donbas
 Hafi ya Severodonetsk, Bakhmut ni igisagara kiriko kirahekenywa n'intambara buke buke
 Muri ino ndwi kiri nko ku birometero bitanu uvuye aho Abarusiya bageze
 Mu ndwi iza bafise kuba bari hafi yaco
 Abasivire bafise iyo baja baragiye
 Mu bihomoka i Donbas, intsinzi i Kyiv muri Ntwarante (3) - yaranzwe n'umunerezo, icubahiro n'ukwitanga -  iri kure
 Bakhmut yaratewe amabombe bikomeye
 Ahagaze imbere y'inzu yiwe yabomotse, umugabo ari mu myaka 40 yitwa Mitri ntaco bimubwira, ariko akaba yuzuye umwikomo n'ishavu
 Ntabona ico yiteze mu gisagara ciwe
 "Jewe si ndi Nostradamus
 Kubera iki Putin yateye? Vyose ni imikino ya poritike"
 Mitri avuga ko uwo Perezida  Zelensky yasubiriye Petro Poroshenko aba yaramaze gushika ku masezerano yo guhagarika intambara ubu
 "N'imiburiburi imbere y'aha hari amahoro, hari ibiganiro vyariko biraba
 Birababaje kubona abantu bariko barapfa, abasirikare
 Birateye isoni"
 Avuga ko ryabaye ikosa rya Perezida Zelensky
 Yaratakaje akaryo keza
 Mitri yadugije ibitugu yinywera agatabi ashavuye cane igihe nari ndamubajije nimba ashobora kwemera amasezerano yokwemerera Uburusiya kugenzura Donbas yose, igereranywa hafi n'ica gatatu c'ubutaka bwagenzura imbere y'iki gitero
 "Sinzi
 None vyohindura iki kuri jewe? Igikuru ni ugukiza igufa
 Iyi ni intango, akataraza kari mu nyuma
 Ni twahakura agatwe, tuzoraba ingene bizogenda"
 Ibihumbi n'ibihumbi vy'abasivire baracari i Severodonetsk mu gihe Abarusiya barwana kugira bagote ingabo za nyuma i Luhansk, mu buraruko bwa Donbas
 Ku gituro ca gari ya moshi i Pokrovsk, kure y'ahabera urugamba hatekanye, navuganye na Lida, umutamakazi agendera ku gakinga k'abamugaye
 Hari haciye akanya avanywe muri Severodonetsk
 Ari kumwe n'abandi basivire bamugaye n'abakomeretse, yariko ahungishirizwa mu karere gatekanye mu burengero bwa Ukraine hakoreshejwe i tereni idasanzwe, yahinduwe rusehabaniha kandi ifise n'abajejwe kuvura indembe bo mw'ishirahamwe ry'Abaganga Batagira Imbibe, MSF
 Lida, yerekana ko ataco bimubwiye yinywera n'itabi, yarokowe n'abasirikare bamuhungishije ari kumwe n'abandi basivire, baca mu turere twacucagiwe bikomeye amabombe
 "Ibintu vyose vyatewe amabombe, sinzi ingene twarokotse
 Ibiyo vyarasambutse, ibintu vyose birasanzaye
 Kandi sinshobora kugendagenda
 Namugaye
 Uko niko ibintu bimeze
 "Inzu y'igorofa icenda, amagorofa yo hejuru yarabomowe
 Vyose vyarasenyuwe
 "Putin ni umuhimbiri
 Twari tubayeho mu mahoro
 Harabayeyo Ubumwe bw'Abasoviyeti, ni bibe uko
 Baratandukanije Ukraine n'Uburusiya
 Rero aho niho ingorane zatanguriye"
 Mu gihe ingabo za Putin zoshobora kugota Severodonetsk, ivyo ari vyo vyose hoca hakurikira ibisagara bikomakomeye vya Kramatorsk na Slovyansk mu ntara ya Donetsk, ku rundi ruhande rwa Donbas
 Hanyuma ashobora guca atangaza intsinzi mu ntambara yo kurwanira Donbas
 Nabonye iyindi myobo yari iherutse kwimbwa hafi y'ibi bisagara, mu gihe ingabo za Ukraine zariko zitegura ibindi birindiro zishobora guhungirako
 Mu gihe ibi bisagara vyofatwa n'ingabo z'Uburusiya, ariko zishobora kutabishikako kuko vyompi biracungerewe bikomeye, Perezida Putin ashobora gutangaza intsinzi ya mbere ikomeye muri ino ntambara
 Uburusiya bwoca bugenzura akarere k'urubibe rwo ku ruhande rw'ubumanuko kuva i Donbas hamwe n'urubibe hafi rwose rwa Ukraine
 Perezida Zelensky avuga ko ibiganiro vyonyene ari vyo bishobora kurangiza intambara, ariko akavuga ko Uburusiya butegerezwa gusubira ku birindiro bwari bufise imbere y'intambara
 Incuti ziwe, zirongowe na Amerika n'Ubwongereza, bashaka ko Putin atakaza inguvu burundu
 Bavuga ko Uburusiya kizira ko butsinda intambara
 Abakeba babo bavuga ko bazorwana gushika ku munya-Ukraine wa nyuma
 Igiciro c'intambara ni amaraso
 Mu gihe imiryango iriko irahamba abayo bapfuye, abanya Ukraine benshi, nka Mitri i Bakhmut, bazokwama babaza igiciro c'amaraso bariko barasesa, hanyuma babaze nimba bakwiye guheba ubutaka canke ubuzima kugira ngo intambara ihagarare

Umusatirizi wa  Liverpool Mohamed Salah avuga ko "ivyo ari vyo vyose" mu mwaka w'inkino uza azoba ari muri Liverpool, ariko ko adashaka kujanwa mu mpari z'amasezerano mashasha
 Amasezerano ya Salah azorangira muri Ruheshi (6) 2023, ibituma haduka amajambo menshi ko ashobora kugurishwa mu gihe atotera igikumu ku masezerano mashasha kuko inyuma y'umwaka yoca yigira ahandi ata rufaranga na rumwe aguzwe
 Abajijwe kuri kazoza kiwe imbere y'urukino rwa nyuma rwa Ligue des Champions/Champions League ku wa gatandatu, avuga ati: "Si nshaka kuvuga kuri ibi bintu
 "Ico nipfuza ni ukubona Hendo [Jordan Henderson] ateruye igikombe"
 Uyu musatirizi w'umunyamisiri w'imyaka 29 avuga kandi ati: "Sinitaho ivy'amasezerano ubu
 Si nshaka kwigungirako
 "Ivyo ari vyo vyose ndacari ng'aha mu mwaka uza w'inkino"
 Mugenziwe Sadio Mane, wewe avuga ko azoshikiriza ingingo ku bijanye na kazoza kiwe inyuma y'urukino rwa nyuma na  Real Madrid i Paris
 Uyu mukinyi mpuzamakungu wa Sénégal  amaze kwinjiriza ibitsindo 120 mu nkino 268 amaze gukinira Liverpool, na we nyene mu kwa gatandatu yinjira mu mezi 12 ya nyuma y'amasezerano yiwe
 Yabwiye imboneshakure Sky Sports News ati: "Iki kibazo [kuri kazoza kanje] nzocishura inyuma ya Champions League
 Nimba nzoguma aha canke ntazoguma aha, nzovyishura inyuma ya Champions League"
 Umumenyereza wa Liverpool Jurgen Klopp ntabona ko ibizova mu rukino rwo ku wa gatandatu ari rwo fatiro ku bakinyi bamwe bamwe mu gufata ingingo yo kwongereza amasezerano canke kuyahagarika
 Ati: "Oya, oya na gato
 None, mu gihe twotsinda, boca bashaka kugenda ? Turiko turaganira n'abakinyi bose, ubu si igihe co kuvuga ibijanye n'ivyavuye muri ibi biganiro
 Nta n'umwe azi ivyo turiko turategura
 "Gusa nta mwanya uhari, buri misi itatu turakina
 Abakinyi barabizi, turabizi, rimwe na rimwe turahuza, ikindi gihe ntiduhuze, hanyuma rero tugakorera hamwe
 "Turazinanye kuva kera"
 Salah yinjiye muri Liverpool avuye muri Roma mu 2017 akaba amaze kwinjiza ibitsindo 156 mu nkino 253 amaze gukinira Liverpool
 Yarafashije uyu murwi gutsindira ihiganwa ry'Ubwongereza (Premier League) mu 2019-2020, igikombe c'ihiganwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere iwabo (Champions League) mu 2019, igikombe FA Cup hamwe n'igikombe c'ihiganwa (League Cup) uno mwaka w'inkino, igikombe c'isi yose gihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere  (FIFA Club World Cup)  be n'igikombe ca Uefa Super Cup mu kiringo amaze muri Liverpool
 Mu kwa gatatu, Klopp yavuze ko Salah ari we wenyene azofata ingingo ku vyerekeye  gutera igikumu ku masezerano mashasha
 Uyu musatirizi yahoze akinira Chelsea aherutse kuvuga ko ashaka kuguma muri Liverpool, ariko ko kazoza kiwe kari mu minwe y'uyu murwi kandi ko atariko arasaba "ibitagenda"
 Ku wa Mungu, Liverpool yarangije ihiganwa ry'Ubwongereza isumbijwe inota rimwe ritarenga ntirirenguke na Manhester City, ivyarangije ibizigizigi bari bafise vyo gutsindira ibikombe bine mu mwaka w'inkino umwe, ibitarigera bibaho mu Bwongereza
 Urukino rwo ku wa gatandatu ruzoyihuza na Real Madrid i Paris mu Bufaransa ruzokwibutsa urundi rwa Champions League rwo mu 2018 aho uyo murwi wo muri Espagne watsinze 3-1, Salah akaba atarurangije kubera yavunitse mu gice ca mbere agonganye na Sergio Ramos mu buryo bwateje impari nyinshi
 Salah yongerako ati: "Numva mfise ishaka, ishaka ryinshi cane, inyuma y'ivyabaye igihe giheze [mu rukino rwa nyuma rwa 2018], kandi ku wa Mungu - bose bafise ishaka kuri iki"
 "Iki turakirwanira kandi bose barabishashaye"

Abana 19 n'abigisha babiri barapfuye ku wa kabiri w'iyi ndwi kw'ishure ry'intango riri mu gisagara ca Uvalde mu ntara ya Texas, inyuma y'aho umusore w'imyaka 18 yinjiye afise inkoho agatangura kubarasa
 Uyu musore yamenyekanye kw'izina rya Salvador Ramos, ni umunyamerika yaba muri ico gisagara kibamwo abantu 15
000 kiri ku birometero 135 uvuye mu gisagara ca San Antonio
 Buramatari wa Texas Greg Abbott avuga ko uyu musore yapfuye inyuma yo kurasana n'abapolisi kuri iryo shure
 Abapolisi babiri barakomeretse ariko Abbott avuga ko batababaye cane
 Abarashwe ni abanyeshure biga mu wa 2, 3 na 4 bari hagati y'imyaka 7 na 10
 Abigisha babiri kandi barishwe barashwe n'uyu musore kuri iryo shure ry'abana bashika 500, hafi bose bakaba bafise amamuko muri Amerika y'Epfo
 Icateye ubu bukozi bw'ikibi ntikiramenyekana, ariko igipolisi kivuga ko ibimenyetso vyose vyerekana ko Ramos yabikoze wenyene
 Uyu musore yariko anyonga imodoka itwara imizigo yatembagariye mu mufurege ku metero nkeya uvuye kw'ishure ry'intango rya Robb, ari ho yaca yinjira agatangura kurasa
 Umukozi wo mu gisata kijejwe gucungera imbibe yari hafi igihe ivyo vyaba yaciye yinjira muri iryo shure aca aramurasa aramwica, nk'uko vyandikwa n'itororokanirizo ry'amakuru Associated Press
 Nyene gukora aka kabi, yambaye umwambaro umukingira amasasu igihe yakora iki gitero, yavuye muri iyo modoka yari yatembagariye mu mufurege afise inkoho hanyuma aca atangura kurasa muri iyo nyubakwa, nk'uko Sereja (sergeant) Erick Estrada wo mu gisata kijejwe umutekano muri Texas yabibwiye CNN
 Abajejwe amatohoza bavuga ko nyene gukora ibi yari afise inkoho izwi nka AR-15, irekura amasasu menshi kandi ifise igikono (magazine) kijamwo amasasu menshi
 Yari aherutse kwuzuza imyaka 18 y'amavuka ariko ntiyari azwi mu bukozi bw'ikibi, nk'uko bivugwa n'abategetsi
 Ramos yari yaguze inkoho zibiri zo mu bwoko bwa AR n'amasasu 375 imisi mike imbere yo gushikana imyaka 18, nk'uko biri mu cegeranyo igipolisi c'akarere carungikiye umukenguzamateka Whitmire
 Imwe muri izo nkoho yatowe ahabereye iri bara, n'ibikono indwi vy'amasasu 30 kimwe kimwe, iyindi nayo ikaba yatowe mu modoka yiwe yatembagariye hanze y'iri shure, nk'uko ico cegeranyo kibivuga
 Ibinyamakuru vya Amerika birasigura ubuzima n'inyifato y'uyu musore yakoze iki gitero, aho bamwe mu runganwe rwiwe bavuga ko yari umusore nyamwigendako yakorewe itotezwa
 Umunyeshure yigeze kuba umugenzi wa Ramos mu mwaka w'umunani yabwiye ikinyamakuru Washington Post ko yari umusore afise isoni yama ariko atazomerwa n'abanyeshure bagenziwe, bimwe mu vyabituma kukaba kwari uko yavuga agigimiza kandi avugira uburevi
 Avuga ko uyu musore yigeze gukinana na we udukino tw'amareresi nka Fortnite na Call of Duty, yahavuye atangura kwerekana impinduka mu mibereho yiwe mbere aca atangura kugira inyifato zidasanzwe nko kw'ikebagura mu maso
 Yemeza kandi ko uyu mugenzi wiwe yaciye atangura kwambara impuzu zibabura tsikiri n'ibirato vya gisirikare, mbere atangura no kuza arasiba mw'ishure igihe kirekire, kandi bigasa n'uko atari kurangiza amashure
 Ku ruhande rwiwe, umubanyi wa Ramos w'imyaka 41  yabwiye CBS, ikinyamakuru co muri Amerika gikorana na BBC, ko Ramos "yari afise ubuzima bugoye", kandi ko nyina wiwe yari yariziziwe n'ibiyayuramutwe kandi ko "atigeze yerekana" ko amwitayeho
 Avuga kandi ko kuva ku myaka 14 canke 15 inyifato yiwe yahindutse, ko bitari vyoroshe kuganira nawe mbere biboneka ko "n'ishure ryamutaye"
 Ivyabona bivuga ko uyu musore yavugana ku mbuga hwaniro n'abantu yamenyanye nabo ku mbuga ngurukanabumenyi
 Imbere yo kuva muhira, uyu musore yabanje kurasa inakuru wiwe mu maso maze ajanwa kwa muganga ameze nabi cane
 Amakuru yerekana ko Ramos yaba aho i Uvalde kandi ko yahoze yiga mw'ishure ryisumbuye ryari hafi y'aho
 Yari afise impapuro ziranga aho inakuru yaba nk'aho na we nyene yaba, nk'uko biri mu nzandiko zahawe ikigo kijejwe kugenzura inzoga, itabi, ibirwanisho bicira umuriro n'ibisasu (Federal Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives)
 Nk'uko bivugwa na buramatari Abbott, Ramos yanditse ubutumwa butatu ku rubuga rwiwe rwa Facebook imbere y'uko akora iki gitero
 Mu butumwa bwa mbere yanditse hasigaye nk'iminota 30, yanditse ati:  "Ngiye kurasa nyokuru"
 Mu bwa kabiri, yemeje ko yabikoze
 Mu bwa gatatu, hasigaye nk'iminota 15 imbere y'uko akora iki gitero kw'ishure, yatangaje ko yari agiye kurasa kw'ishure ry'intango
 'Ntiyari umuntu w'amahane' Nyina w'uyu musore yagize ico avuga ku mwana wiwe yagandaguye abantu 21
 Adriana Reyes yabwiye ikinyamakuru Daily Mail ati: "Umwana wanje ntiyari umuntu w'induru
 Ndatangajwe n'ibi bintu yakoze"
 Reyes arahakana amakuru avuga ko yari afitaniye imigenderanire mibi n'umwana wiwe
 Yabwiye iki kinyamakuru ati: "Nari mfitaniye imigenderanire myiza nawe
 Yarikumiriye, nta bagenzi benshi yari afise"
 Reyes w'imyaka 39 yabwiye kandi ikinyamakuru NBC News ati: "Numva ibintu vyose bimbabaje
 Ni ibintu vyinshi vyabaye, ariko ubu numva ntameze neza"
 Juan Alvarez, umugenzi wa Reyes, yabwiye NBC ko uyu musore yakoze iri bara yari "umuntu atangaje"
 Ati: "Sinari bwigere numvikana nawe
 Sinari bwigere nifatanya nawe
 Nta muntu n'umwe bavugana"
 "Utanguye kuvugana nawe, wicara gusa ukavamwo ukagenda"

Abana b'inzoya cumi n'umwe baguye mu muriro wadutse mu bitaro mu gisagara ca  Tivaouane kiri mu burengero bwa Senegal, nk'uko vyavuzwe n'umukuru w'ico gihugu, Macky Sall
 Amakuru ya mbere yavuze ko uwo muriro wavuye ku ngorane z'umuyagankuba (court circuit/short circuit), ku bw'abanyaporitike aho muri Senegal
 Inzoya zitatu zarashoboye kurokorwa, nk'uko vyemezwa n'umukuru w'igisagara, Demba Diop Sy
 Imiryango yashitse ku bitaro vya  Mame Abdou Aziz Sy Dabakh kuraba ko abana bayo barokotse
 Bamwe barengewe n'agahinda igihe bumva ivyabaye
 Moustapha Cissé yabwiye Reuters ko umwana w'uwo bavukana yari amaze indwi zitatu, Mohamed, ari mu bapfuye
 Umuvyeyi  Ramata Gueye  yapfuye ahejeje kuvyara
 We n'umugabo wiwe, El Hadj Gueye, bari bamaze imyaka bagerageza kuronka umwana, Mohamed  akaba yari we mwana wabo  umwe rudende
 Bwana Cissé yagize ati: "Birakomeretsa ku mutima kubona abuze umugore n'umwana akivuka
 Sinshobora no kumuraba mu maso
 "None ni umugambi w'Imana canke ni kubera ibitaro vyo muri Senegal vyananiwe? Iki kibazo dutegerezwa kugishikiriza leta"
 Ibi bitaro vyaheruka kwugururwa vuba, nk'uko ibiro ntaramakuru AFP bibivuga, bibikuye mu bitangazamakuru vyo muri Senegal
 Prezida Macky Sall yatangaje ikigandaro c'iminsi itatu
 Ku butumwa kuri Twitter yanditse ati "Abavyeyi babo n'imiryango, ndabahojeje bivuye ku mutima
" Ndeye Absa Gueye, mu nyuma nawe yahavuye asanga yaburiyemwo umwuzukuru yavuze ati: "Numvise inkuru y'uwo muriro nijoro, ariko sinabwira umukobwa wanje
 Narindiriye ko buca kugira ndamubwire"
 Umwe mu baba Tivaouane, Ousmane Kane, yabwiye Reuters ati: "Ibi biradukomeretsa nk'abanya-Senegal twese"
 Nawe umushikiranganji ajejwe amagara y'abantu  Abdoulaye Diouf Sarr yanditse ari Geneve mu nama y'ishami rya ONU rijejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi OMS  ati: "Birababaje cane kubona ibintu nk'ibi vyashitse"
 Yaciye amenyesha ko hatanguye amatohoza  kandi ko agiye guhagarika ivyo yari arimwo kugira yihute gusubira mu gihugu buno nyene
 Ivyashitse vyashegeshe abantu ku mbuba hwaniro bidogera ingene bitabwaho mu bijanye n'amagara
 Umushingamateka atavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi  Mamadou Lamine Diallo yaneguye reta mu kwandika kuri twitter ati: "Izindi nzoya zahiriye mu bitaro vy'igihugu… Ibi ntawovyihanganira"
 Ishirahamwe riharanira agateka ka zina muntu Amnesty International ryasavye reta gushiraho umugwi wigenga wo gukora amatohoza kugira hamenyekane ababifisemwo uruhara hanyuma bahanwe, hatarabwe urugero bariko mu butegetsi bw'igihugu
 Amnesty yasavye kandi ko ivyumba vyose vy'abana bavutse bataragera bisuzumwa, mu gihe ibintu nk'ivyo vyari bimaze gushika mu gisagara kiri mu buraruko ca  Linguère mu mwaka uheze
 Ico gihe abana  bane bavutse batageze barapfuye inyuma y'aho umuriro wadukiye mu gice c'abavyeyi c'ivyo bitaro
 Ico gihe umukuru w'igisagara yavuze ko hari habaye ikibazo c'umuyagankuba  mu cuma co gutanga akayaga  co mu cumba c'abavyaye
 Ivyashitse ku wa gatatu bishitse kandi hamaze iminsi hari ishavu ryinshi  mu gihugu kubera urupfu rw'umugore yari ku gise,  Astou Sokhna, yapfuye nk'uko bivugwa ariko arasaba ko yokorwa (yobagwa) kugira avyare,   mu kiringo c'amasaha 20 yamaze ari ku nda gushika aho apfa
 N'umwana yari mu nda nawe nyene yarapfuye

Abana 19 hamwe n'abandi bakuze babiri biciwe mu gitero c'umusore yitwaje inkoho kw'ishure ry'intango  riri mu bumanuko bw'intara ya Texas
 Uyu musore w'imyaka 18 yateye ishure ry'intango rya Robb (Robb Elementary School) mu gisagara ca Uvalde imbere y'uko yicwa n'abajejwe umutekano, nk'uko bivugwa n'abategetsi
 Abajejwe amatohoza bavuga ko nyene gukora ibi yari afise inkoho y'i basitola (pistolet) izwi nka AR-15, irekura amasasu menshi kandi ifise igikono (magazine) kijamwo amasasu menshi
 Uyu musore azwi ko yabanje kurasa inakuru imbere y'uko yiha inkumbi
 Ibinyamakuru vy'akarere bivuga ko ashobora kuba yize amashure yisumbuye muri ako karere
 Umukuru w'igipolisi ca Uvalde, Pete Arredondo avuga ko uyu musore yuguruye umucanwa isaha 11:32 ku wa kabiri mu masaha yo muri Texas (isaha imwe n'iminota 32 z'ijoro mu masaha yo mu Burundi no mu Rwanda), kandi ko abajejwe amatohoza bemeza ko "iki caha c'inzigo yagikoze ari umwe"
 Buramatari wa Texas  Greg Abbott avuga ko uwakoze iki gitero yataye imodoka imbere yo kwinjira mw'iryo shure gukora iki gitero "c'ubugome, kidatahuritse"
 Umwe muri abo bakuze yishwe yari umwigisha ibinyamakuru vya Amerika vyita Eva Mireles
 Urupapuro rwiwe ku rubuga ngurukanabumenyi rw'iryo shure ruvuga ko yari afise umukobwa yiga mu mashure yisumbuye
 Abanyeshure badashika 500 nibo biga kuri iryo shure rirwiriyemwo abanyeshure bo mu bwoko bw'aba Hispanic riri ku birometero vyababa 135 mu burengero bw'igisagara ca San Antonio
 Itororokanirizo ry'amakuru Associated Press rivuga ko umukozi wo mu gisata kijejwe gucungera imbibe yari hafi yaciye yinjira muri iryo shure aca yica uyo musore yakoze iki gitero
 Uvalde iri ku birometero bidashika 128 uvuye ku rubibe rwa Mexique, ikaba ifise ikirindiro c'ingabo zikora mu gisata kijejwe gucungera imbibe
 Babiri mu bakozi b'iki gisata bavugwa ko barashwe mu gihe bariko bararasana n'uyu musore yari afise inkoho
 Umwe muri bo yarashwe mu mutwe nk'uko abategetsi babivuga, bakongerako y'uko bompi bameze neza aho bariko baravurirwa mu bitaro
 Nk'uko bivugwa n'ikinyamakuru CBS News, uyu musore yari yambaye umwambaro umukingira amasasu igihe yakora iki gitero
 Uwundi musore nawe nyene w'imyaka 18 yikekwa gukora igitero ku kaguriro k'imfungurwa i Buffalo, muri New york, ku wa 14 Rusama (5) na we nyene yari yambaye umwambaro umukingira amasasu kandi afise n'inkoho irasa amasasu menshi - izi nkoho zompi zikaba zidandazwa muri Amerika
 Ibitaro Uvalde Memorial Hospital vyanditse ku rubuga rwa Facebook ko abana 13 bashikanywe ku bitaro "hakoreshejwe za rusehabaniha n'amabisi (bus)"
 Abarongoye ibitaro vya kaminuza bavuga ko umugore w'imyaka 66 n'umukobwa w'imyaka 10 basinzikaye cane aho bariko baravurirwa mu bitaro i San Antonio
 Mu mihana yegereye iri shure ry'intango rya Robb, habaye uguteramira abaguye muri iki gitero n'abarokotse
 Ijwi rya Karla Bohman ryacitse aho yariko abwira abari aho ko hari umuryango w'umugenzi utazi amakuru y'umukobwa wabo, akaba yari umunyeshure kw'iryo shure
 N'amarira, Bohman yavuze ati: "Ntibazi nimba ari mu cumba c'inkomere canke nimba ari umwe mu bapfuye, ariko barazi ko iki gitero camugizeko ingaruka uburyo ubu canke buriya
 Sindavyumva!" Cheryl Juhasz amaze ubuzima bwose aba i Uvalde, yakoroye amosozi muri ico gisabisho
 "Biragoye gutahura akabi nk'aka
 Aho vyobera hose, ariko biragoye iyo bibereye muhira"
 Mw'ijambo yashikirije, Perezida  Joe Biden avuga ko yacitse intege kandi ko yaruhishijwe no kwama ariko aravuga ku bijanye n'abarasa abantu mu kivunga, aca asaba ko inkoho zocungerwa
 "Uribaza abana babonye ivyabaye - babona abagenzi bapfa, nk'uko umengo bari mu ntambara, izina ry'Imana! Ibi bizobagumamwo ubuzima bwabo bwose"
 Yategetse ko amabendera yo kuri Maison Blanche/White House n'ayo ku nyubakwa za reta ya Amerika aduzwa gushika hagati mu kwibuka abaguye muri iki gitero i Uvalde
 Umusi wa nyuma w'ukwiga kuri iri shure wari ejo ku wa kane
 Ariko ivyigwa n'ibikorwa vyose vyaciye bihagarikwa mu kiringo cose cari gisigaye muri uno mwaka
 Ivyo kurasa mu mashure ni ibintu biguma vyibonekeza muri Amerika, aho mu mwaka uheze habaye ibitero 26, nk'uko bivugwa na EdWeek, ikinyamakuru gitangaza amakuru yo muri ico gisata c'indero
 Igitero cabaye mu 2012 kw'ishure ry'intango rya Sandy Hook Elementary School mu ntara ya Connecticut carababaje Abanyamerika
 Abantu 26 nibo baguye muri ico gitero cakozwe n'umusore w'imyaka 20, kigahitana abana bari hagati y'imyaka itanu n'itandatu
 Mw'ijambo yashikirije inama nkenguzamateka nijoro ku wa kabiri, umukenguzamateka w'umu Democrat  Chris Murphy wo mu ntara ya Connecticut yatakambiye bagenziwe gutora itegeko ryo kugenzura inkoho
 Ati: "Turiko dukora iki? Kubera iki turi ng'aha? Nimba atari gutorera umuti ikibazo ciraye nk'iki? Ibi si ukuvuga ko bidashobora guhagarikwa"
 "Aba bana si ukuvuga ko bagize igihamana kibi
 Ibi bintu biba muri iki gihugu honyene
 Nta handi, nta handi abana bato baja kw'ishure bazi ko umusi umwe bashobora kuraswa"
 Ariko umukenguzamateka wa Texas, Ted Cruz, umu Repubulika, ariyamiriza aka kamo ko gucungera inkoho
 Avuga ko kwaka abanyagihugu "uburenganzira bwo gutunga inkoho


 bidakunda
 Ntaco vyomara
 Ntivyobuza abakora ivyaha"
 Ku wa mbere, icegeranyo ca FBI casanze ibitero vy'abantu barasa vyiyongereye incuro zibiri kuva ikiza ca coronavirus cadutse mu 2020

Umunywanyi wa wa muhari wiyita Reta ya ki-Islam (Etat Islamique/Islamic State) yari yateguye kugandagura uwahoze ari umukuru w'igihugu wa Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika George W Bush ariko uwu mugambi ukaba wahinyuwe na FBI, nk'uko bivugwa n'abategetsi ba Amerika
 Uwikekwa, akaba aba muri Ohio, yagirizwa ko yarondeye kwinjiza abarwanyi muri Amerika abavanye muri Mexique kugira bakore iki gitero
 Ubu arapfunzwe, ejo ku wa kabiri akaba yararengukishijwe muri sentare y'igihugu i Ohio
 FBI yakoresheje inderetsi hamwe n'ubuhinga bwo gucungera bwa elektroniki mu gutesha uwu mugambi
 Nk'uko vyerekanwa n'inzandiko zo muri sentare, uyu muntu yikekwa - azwi kw'izina rya Shihab Ahmed Shihab w'imyaka 52 - ni umunyagihugu wa Irak abaye muri Amerika kuva mu 2020 akaba yari akirindiriye ubuhungiro yasavye
 FBI ivuga ko Shihab yabwiye umwizigirwa wiwe, yigize uwinjiza abantu mu buryo bwa magendo, ko yari mu murwi uzwi nka Al-Raed - ijambo ry'icarabu risigura umuturagaro - ufise icicaro muri Qatar
 Mu biganiro yagiranye n'isoko rya FBI,  Shihab avuga ko yashaka kwica George Bush kubera "yishe abanya-Irak benshi" yongera "asambura" Irak
 Avuga kandi ko na we nyene yari kuba muri ico gitero "kandi ntiyaraba ko yari gupfa, kuko yari kuba yishimiye kuba mu bakora ico gitero"
 Shihab avugwa ko yariko arondera ibiranga abapolisi vy'amanyanga kandi ko yariko aratohoza kugira amenye ko abarwanyi biyitirira idini rya Islam bashobora kwinjizwa muri Amerika mu kinyegero baciye ku rubibe rwa Mexique kugira ngo bakore iki gitero, hanyuma bagashobora gusubizwa inyuma mu kubahungisha
 Abantu babiri yari yizeye kwinjiza muri Amerika bavugwa ko bahoze bakora mu gisata c'igendereza ca Irak kandi ko bamenyereye ibitero vyo kugandagura
 Shihab avugwa kandi ko yavuganye n'irindi soko rya FBI yigize umukiriya mu vyo kwinjiza abantu mu kinyegero
 Aba bareretsi bompi bafashe amajwi y'ibiganiro bagiriraniye nawe
 Shihab avugwa ko yabwiye aya masoko ko yari yizeye gukoresha aba bantu mu kwinjiza abanywanyi ba Reta ya ki-Islam muri Amerika, n'aho atagirizwa kuba umunywanyi w'uyu muhari w'iterabwoba
 Igihe kimwe, Shihab n'umwe muri aya masoko barajanye i  Dallas muri Texas gufata amashusho y'umuhana wa Bush hamwe n'ay'ikigo George W
 Bush Institute
 Muri Ntwarante (3) 2022, avugwa ko yakoresheje inama  mw'ihoteri y'i Columbus muri Ohio yo kurondera ibirwanisho n'imyambaro y'amanyanga y'abajejwe umutekano
 Ashobora gucirirwa umunyororo w'imyaka 10 ku caha co kugerageza kwinjiza umuntu muri Amerika bidaciye mu mategeko, hamwe n'iyindi 20 ku caha co gufasha no gukokeza abashaka kugandagura uwahoze ari umutegetsi wa Amerika
 Umuvugizi wa Bush avuga ko uyu yahoze arongoye iki gihugu "yizeye cane amakungu n'igisata ca Amerika kijejwe igendereza, hamwe n'abajejwe umutekano n'ibindi bisata bijejwe igendereza"
 BBC irarindiriye ico FBI ibivugako

Umukozi wo mu biro vy'ubuserukizi bw'Uburusiya yahevye akazi kiwe mu buryo bwo kwiyamiriza ico yita intambara "yo gusesa amaraso, y'ubujuju kandi yatewe na Putin kuri Ukraine"
 Boris Bondarev, urubuga rwa LinkedIn rukaba ruvuga ko yakora mu biro vy'ubuserukizi bw'Uburusiya muri ONU i Genève/Geneva, yabwiye BBC ko yari azi y'uko ingingo yiwe yo kugira ico ashikirije ishobora gusigura ko Kremlin ubu imufata nk'igihemu
 Ariko yaryumyeko mu kuvuga ko iyi ntambara ari "amabi akorerwa abanyagihugu ba Ukraine" hamwe "n'abanyagihugu b'Ubrusiya"
 Moscou ntaco irashikiriza
 Uburusiya ntibwihanganira uwo wese anegura canke ateye kubiri n'ibishikirizwa na reta ku vyerekeye iyi ntambara, ifatwa gusa ko ari "igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare"
 Mw'ikete yacishije ku mbuga hwaniro kandi yahaye abakozi bagenziwe mu biro vy'ubuserukizi, Bondarev asigura ko yafashe ingingo yo guhagarika akazi kiwe yari amazemwo imyaka 20 kubera atashobora "kwihanganira aka gasuzuguro ko gusesa amaraso, katagira insiguro kandi kadakenewe"
 Yandika ati: "Abateguye iyi ntambara bashaka ikintu kimwe gusa - kwihambirira ku butegetsi imyaka yose"
 "Kugira ngo babishikeko, bashaka gutanga ubuzima bw'abantu benshi bashoboka
 Ibihumbi n'ibihumbi vy'Abarusiya n'abanya Ukraine baramaze gupfa kubera ibi"
 Iri kete ntirisiga inyuma uwahoze ari umukoresha wiwe, mu kwagiriza umushikiranganji ajejwe imigenderanire ko arajwe ishinga cane "n'ibinyoma n'inzigo" gusumba ibikorwa vyiwe nk'uwujejwe imigenderanire
 Uravye amakete yo gutanga imihoho, iri ni agahomerabunwa
 Uyu mu diplomate  Boris Bondarev ntarya umunwa mu kunegura Perezida Putin, umushikiranganji w'imigenderanire Lavrov hamwe n'igitero c'Uburusiya kuri Ukraine
 "Intambara y'ubugome


icaha c'agahomerabunwa


ugukokeza intambara, ibinyoma n'urwanko


" Ni ibintu bidakunze kuba kwumva amajambo nk'aya ku mutegetsi w'Umurusiya
 Muri ano mezi atatu kuva Putin atanguje ico gushika ubu yita "igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare" muri Ukraine (ico isi hafi yose yita intambara y'Uburusiya), ni ibimenyetso bike vy'abatishimiye inzego z'Uburusiya
 Vyoba ari ibiterasoni ku bategetsi b'Uburusiya? Nivyo
 Barakunze kwerekana ko Abarusiya bose bashigikiye ingingo ya Putin yo gutera Ukraine
 Gusa, umuntu umwe atanze imihoho ntibisigura ko hari abandi bagiye gukurikira
 Bondarev  yemeza ko ari mu nkehwa
 Yemeza ko ubu abakozi hafi bose mu bushikiranganji bw'imigenderanire y'Uburusiya bashigikiye reta kandi ko bashigikiye 'igikorwa kidasanzwe' ca Kremlin
 Avugana na BBC,  Bondarev yavuze ko ata "yindi nzira yabona" atari ugutanga imihoho: "Sinibaza ko hari ico izohindura kinini, ariko nibaza ko ari agatafari gato mu ruhome runini cane rushobora kuzokwubakwa
 Ni vyo nizeye"
 Bondarev yavuze ko mu ntango bagenziwe bakiriye iki gitero "n'umunezero udasanzwe"
 Yabwiye BBC ati: "Ubu bafise umunezero muke, kubera turi mu ngorane, ubwa mbere na mbere zishingiye ku butunzi
 Ariko simbona ko hari benshi bashobora kwigarura bagahindura imbono yabo"
 Ati: "Barashobora guhinduka buke buke, bakagabanya uburakari, ariko ntibumve amahoro"
 Ku ruhande rwiwe, Bondarev avuga ko atari bwigere yumva "isoni ku gihugu canje" nk'izo yagize ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), umusi igitero gitangura
 Ntibizwi nimba ari we mu diplomate wa mbere atanze imihoho muri ubwo buserukizi, na rirya ata wundi yari bwigere arisohora
 Bondarev nta nkeka afise ko Moscou igiye kumufata nk'igihemu, ariko akavuga ko ata kintu na kimwe yakoze giteye kubiri n'amategeko
 Ati: "Natanze imihoho gusa nshikiriza n'akari ku mutima
 Ariko ni ngombwa ko ngira impungenge ku mutekano wanje"

Umukinyi wa Manchester City Benjamin Mendy yahakanye ivyaha icenda bishingiye ku gitsina yagirizwa ko yakoreye abagore batandatu
 Imbere ya Sentare ya Chester Crown, Mendy w'imyaka 27 aba ahitwa Prestbury mu karere ka Cheshire, yahakanye ivyaha vyose yagirizwa, harimwo indwi vyo gufata ku nguvu
 Uyu mukinyi mpuzamakungu w'Umufaransa yagirizwa kandi ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina no kugerageza gusambanya ku nguvu
 Bivugwa ko ibi vyaha vyabereye i muhira iwe hagati ya Gitugutu (10) 2018 na Myandagaro (8) 2021
 Uyu yagirizwa yiteze gucirirwa urubanza ku wa 25 Mukakaro (7) 2022
 Uwo bagirizwa hamwe Louis Saha Matturie, aba ahitwa Eccles mu karere ka Salford, na we nyene yahakanye ivyaha 12 yagirizwa
 Uyu mugabo w'imyaka 40 ahakana ivyaha umunani vyo gufata ku nguvu hamwe n'ibindi bine vy'ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina, yagirizwa ko yakoreye abagore umunani hagati ya Mukakaro (7) 2012 na Myandangaro (8) 2021
 Bompi babandanya bidegemvya vy'agateganyo
 Inyuma yo kwagirizwa ibi vyaha, Mendy yaciye ahagarikwa vy'agateganyo gukinira umurwi wiwe wa Manchester City inyuma y'inkino 50 za Premier League yari amaze kuyikinira kuva yinjiye muri uwo murwi avuye muri Monaco mu 2017, akaba amaze kandi gukinira Ubufaransa inkino cumi

