Reta ya Ukraine ivuga ko itazokwemera amasezerano y'amahoro n'Uburusiya arimwo ivyo kubuhebera ubutaka
 Iyi ngingo isa n'ukwihagararako kwa Ukraine ije inyuma y'umusi umwe Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky avuze ko inzira yonyene yo guhagarika iyi ntambara ari ibiganiro
 Umuhanuzi w'umukuru w'iki gihugu Mykhaylo Podolyak avuga ko mu gihe Ukraine yogira ivyo iheba vyotuma Uburusiya bukora igitero gikomeye kandi cosesa amaraso menshi
 Avuze aya majambo mu gihe Uburusiya bubandanya bugerageza kugota ingabo za Ukraine ziriko zirarwanira Severodonetsk mu buseruko
 Mu yandi makuru, umukuru w'igihugu ca Pologne Andrzej Duda yabaye umutegetsi wa mbere mvamakungu ashikirije ijambo inama nshingamateka ya Ukraine amaso mu yandi
 Yakomewe amashi menshi igihe yavuga ko abanya Ukraine bonyene ari bo bazokwihitiramwo kazoza kabo
 Yongerako y'uko Pologne izokora ivyo ishoboye vyose mu gufasha Ukraine kwinjira mw'ishirahamwe ry'Ubumwe bwa Bulaya
 Hagati aho, umushikiranganji w'Ubufaransa ajejwe ibibazo vya Bulaya, Clément Beaune, yavuze ko bishobora gufata nk'imyaka "15 cane 20" kugira ngo Ukraine yemererwe nk'umunywanyi w'ishirahamwe ry'Ubumwe bwa Bulaya
 Mu gihe intambara zibandanya, ibiro bikuru vy'igisirikare ca Ukraine bivuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya ziriko ziragerageza kumera uruhome rw'ingabo za Ukraine kugira ngo zishike ku mbibe z'intara ya Luhansk mu buseruko
 Buramatari wa Luhansk, Serhiy Haidai, avuga ko Uburusiya bwagerageje kumenera muri Severodonetsk buciye mu mpande zine zitandukanye
 Mu butumwa yacishije kuri Telegram, yavuze ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zagerageje bikazita ku w'amazi, ariko ko zibandanya zicucagira ibibombe mu turere turimwo imihana y'abantu
 Yongerako y'uko ikiraro gifatanya iki gisagara n'ikindi cegeranye naco ca Lysychansk  cabomowe
 BBC ntiyashoboye guhinyuza ivyo avuga
 Hari ibihugu bimwe bimwe vyo mu Burengero bisaba ko hoba amasezerano yo guhagarika intambara yotuma ingabo z'Uburusiya ziguma mu turere tumwe tumwe zimaze kwigarurira mu bumanuko no mu buseruko bwa Ukraine kuva Moscou iteye iki gihugu ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2)
 Ku wa kane w'indwi iheze, umushikiranganji wa mbere w'Ubutaliyano, Mario Draghi yabwiye inama nkenguzamateka y'igihugu ko "hategerezwa kuba amasezerano yo guhagarika intambara vuba bishoboka"
 Ariko wa muvugizi wa Perezida Zelensky, Mykhaylo Podolyak, avuga ko iyo ngendo yogira ingaruka mbi
 Ati: "Intambara ntizohagarara
 Kazoba agahengwe k'umwanya muto
 Bazoca batanguza ikindi gitero, mbere kizosesa amaraso menshi kandi gikomeye"
 Umunyamakuru wa BBC i Kyiv Joe Inwood avuga ko muri kino gihe Uburusiya na Ukraine bitarahuriza hagati ku vyo kimwe kimwe cose gishobora kwemera
 Avuga ko mu gihe buri ruhande rukibona ko rugifise amahirwe yo kubandanya intambara, ibiganiro bisa n'ibidashoboka

Umukuru w'ishirahamwe rijejwe amagara y'abantu kw'isi (OMS/WHO)  agabisha ko isi ihanganye n'ibibazo "bitoroshe", harimwo Covid, intambara yo muri Ukraine hamwe na monkeypox/variole du singe
 Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yashikirije ibi mw'ijambo yavugiye i Genève/Geneva, aho abahinga b'iri shami rya ONU rijejwe amagara y'abantu bariko baganira ku ngwara y'icaduka ya monkeypox/variole du singe (ubundi variole mu kirundi n'ikinyarwanda ni ibihara, monkey/singe nayo ni inkende), imaze kwibonekeza mu bihugu 15 hanze ya Afrika
 Abantu barenga 80 nibo bamaze kumenyekana ko banduye iyi ndwara i Bulaya, muri Amerika, Canada, Australia na Israel
 Hagati aho, ingaruka ku banyagihugu benshi bivugwa ko zikiri hasi
 Monkeypox/variole du singe - umugera ukunze kwibonekeza mu turere two mu misozi muri Afrika yo hagati n'iy'uburengero  - isa n'uko itoroherwa gukwirakwira hagati y'abantu kandi mu bisanzwe ni indwara itabangamye
 Abantu bose bandura iyi ndwara bakira mu ndwi nkeya, nk'uko bivugwa n'ikigo c'Ubwongereza kijejwe amagara y'abantu, NHS
 Iki kiza cahababuye abahinga, Ubwongereza bukaba bwasohoye ibwirizwa rishasha, aho buvuga ko abikekwa ko babonanye n'abanduye bokwitaramura mu kiringo c'indwi zitatu
 Ku wa gatanu, Ububirigi cabaye igihugu ca mbere catangaje ikiringo c'indwi zitatu co kwitaramura ku bantu banduye
 Ikinyamakuru Guardian kivuga ko mu Bwongereza hitezwe ko abandi banduye batangazwa kuri uno wa mbere
 Mw'ijambo ryo kwugurura ikoraniro ry'ishiraahamwe OMS arongoye ku wa Mungu, Dr Tedros yavuze ati: "Ni vyo koko, ikiza karanda ca Covid si co kibazo conyene gihanze isi yacu
 "Muri kano kanya turiko turavuga bagenzacu kw'isi yose bahanganye n'ibiza vya Ebola muri Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo, monkeypox n'indwara y'igitigu tutazi ico ivako hamwe n'ibibazo vy'imibereho y'abanyagihugu muri Afghanistan, Ethiopia, Somalia, Sudani y'Epfo, Syria, Ukraine na  Yemen
 "Duhanganye n'uruvangatirane rw'indwara, kigoyi n'intambara,  bitewe n'ihindagurika ry'ikirere, ubusumbasumbane n'ugukebana muri poritike z'igihugu"
 OMS yari yavuze ko hari abandi bikekwa kwandura monkeypox bariko bakorwako amatohoza  - ariko akaba ata bihugu yavuze  - ikagabisha ko hashobora gutangazwa n'abandi banduye
 Inyuma y'aho habonekeye umuntu wa mbere yanduye iyi ndwara mu Bwongereza, umugera waciye utangura gutorwa i Bulaya hose - aho ibisata bijejwe amagara y'abantu muri Espagne, Portugal, mu Budagi, mu Bubirigi, mu Bufaransa, mu Buholande, mu Butaliyano no muri Suede vyatangaje ko vyatoye abanduye
 Abandi banduye batangajwe muri Autriche n'Ubuswisi ejo ku wa Mungu
 Igisata kijejwe gukinga indwara mu Bwongereza (Health Security Agency, UKHSA) kivuga ko kimaze gutora abantu 20 banduye gushika ubu, umuhanuzi mukuru waco ajejwe ubuvuzi Dr Susan Hopkins akaba yabwiye ikiganiro Sunday Morning  ca BBC  ati:  "Tubandanya dutora abandi banduye ku musi ku musi"
 Avuga ko uwu mugera uriko urakwiragira mu bantu - aho abatowe banduye batigeze babonana n'umuntu n'umwe yagendeye Afrika y'Uburengero, aho iyi ndwara isanzwe yariraye
 Ariko, Dr Hopkins avuga ko ingaruka ku banyagihugu muri rusangi zikiri "ntoya cane", aho abenshi mu bamaze gusanga baranduye ari abo mu bisagara bimwe bimwe hamwe n'abo muri wa murwi w'abahuza ibitsina babisangiye
 N'aho ata rucanco rwihariye rwa monkeypox ruraboneka, ibihugu bitari bike bivuga ko biriko biregeranya incanco z'ibihara, zikora ku rugero rwa 85% mu gukingira umuntu kuko iyi migera ibiri isa
 Ntibiratomoka neza igitumye iki kiza caduka ubu
 Kimwe mu bishoboka ni uko umugera ufise kuba warihinduye ukuntu, n'aho ata vyemezo bikomeye vy'uko ari umugera wihinduye
 Iyindi nsiguro ni uko umugera wisanze mu kibanza nyaco mu gihe nyaco co kugwirirana
 Monkeypox ishobora kandi kwiyongera mu buryo bworoshe gusumba uko vyari bimeze muri kahise, igihe urucanco rw'ibihara rwakoreshwa ahantu henshi

Sentare muri Ukraine yaciriye urubanza rwo gupfungwa ubuzima bwose umusirikare w'Uburusiya yategeka ikiduga c'intambara kubera kwica umunyagihugu asanzwe mu rubanza rwa mbere rw'ivyaha vyo mu ntambara kuva igitero gitangura
 Uwo musirikare yafatiwe ku rugamba Sgt  Vadim Shishimarin yagiriwe n'icaha ko kwica Oleksandr Shelipov, w'imyaka 62, mu kigwati Chupakhivka co mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko ku wa 28 ukwezi kwa Ruhuhuma(2)
 Yemeye ko yarashe  Shelipov  ariko avuga ko yagendera ku mategeko hanyuma asaba imbabazi umupfakazi w'uwo yishe
 Ibindi vyaha vyinshi vyo mu ntambara biriko birakorwako amatohoza muri Ukraine
 Uburusiya burahakana kuba abasirikare babwo baratose abanyagihugu basanzwe muri ico gitero, n'ubwo hari ivyemezo vyinshi vyerekana igihushane c'ivyo,  mu gihe Ukraine ivuga ko ivyaha birenga 11
000 bishobora kuba bimaze gukorwa
 Ubutegetsi bw'Uburusiya bwavuze ku wa mbere ko butewe impungene n'ivyerekeye umusirikare wabwo kandi ko bugiye kuraba ingene bwomuburanira
 Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov yavuze ko  yamara, Uburusiya ''budafise ubushobozi bwo guhagararira inyungu ziwe amaso mu yandi''
 Ubuserukizi bw'Uburusiya i Kyiv ubu burugaye
 Amuha igihano co gupfungwa ubuzima bwose, umucamanza  Serhiy Agafonov yavuze ko Shishimarin yashize mu ngiro ''itegeko ry'icaha'' ahawe  n'uwumukurira
 ''Kubera icaha cakozwe ari icaha ku mahoro, umutekano, zina muntu n'amategeko mpuzamakungu 


 sentare  ntibona ingene yoca  igihano co gupfungwa kigufi kurusha ico,'' nk'uko yavuze
 Shishimarin, yari yambaye agapira nk'inkofero k'amabara ry'ubururu n'igipfungu (gris), yakurikiye isomwa ry'urubanza ari mu kumba k'ibiyo muri sentare kandi akaba ata kimenyetso yigeze yerekana ko hari ico bimubwiye
 Umushingwamanza wiwe yavuze ko azokwunguruza
 Urwo rubanza rwabereye ku murwa mukuru wa Ukraine, Kyiv, rubonwa nk'akaryo  kuri Ukraine ko kwerekana ko umusikare w'Uburusiya yishe umunyagihugu asanzwe atitayeho amategeko y'intambara
 Imbere y'uko urwo rubanza rusomwa, umushingwamanza wa  Shishimarin -yatanzwe na reta- yabwiye BBC News  ko ko ata mutegetsi w'Uburusiya n'umwe yarondeye ko bavugana
 Igihe uwo muntu yaraswa, Shishimarin w'imyaka 21, n'abandi basirikare bariko bagendera mu mudoka bari bafashe  urukurikirane barimwo rumaze kuraswa hanyuma bagatandukana n'abandi bari kumwe
 Niho babona  Shelipov ariko aravugira kuri terefone, nk'uko  Shishimarin yabwiye sentare
 Avuga ko yaciye abwirwa kumurasa akoresheje inkoho
 Uwumwunganira mu mategeko yabwiye sentare ku wa gatanu ko  Shishimarin  yarashe inyuma y'incuro zibiri yanka amategeko yo kurasa kandi ko rumwe gusa mu masasu atatu cane ane arirwo rwagemye uwo yariko ararasa
 Yavuze ko Shishimarin yarashe kubera ubwoba bw'umutekano wiwe akaba yabajije niba uwo yunganira koko  yari agambiriye kwica
 Mu gihe kimwe c'urubanza, umupfakazi  Kateryna Shelipova yahanganye na  Shishimarin
 Aramubaza ati : "Mbwira, ndagusavye
 Kubera iki baje (Abarusiya) ngaha? Kudungikira? " aho akaba yasubiyemwo ivyavuzwe na prezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin atanga imvo yo gutera Ukraine
 "Mudukingira nde? Mwankingiye umugabo wanje, uwo mwishe?" Uwo musirikare nta nyishu yari afise kuri ivyo bibazo
 Asaba ikigongwe umupfakazi, yavuze ati: " Ariko ndumva ko udashobora kumbabarira
" Madame Shelipova yabwiye BBC ati: "Arambabaje ariko ku caha nk'ico -sinshobora kumubabarira
" Kuva prezida Putin ateye Ukraine ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), nibura abanyagihugu basanzwe 3
838 baramaze kwicwa abandi 4
351 barakomereka, ku bwa ONU
 Mu bishwe harimwo benshi bikekwa ko baguye mu vyaha vyo mu ntambara mu bisagara vyifatiwe n'Uburusiya nka Bucha
 Mu minsi iheze y'uku kwezi nyene, BBC yararonse amasanamu ya CCTV y'iyicwa ry'abanyagihugu basanzwe babiri n'abavugwa ko ari abasirikare b'Uburusiya, urwo rupfu ubu rukaba ruriko ruratohozwa n'abashikirizamanza nk'igishobora kuba ari icaha co mu ntambara

Umumenyereza wa Manchester City Pep Guardiola avuga ko umurwi wiwe ari "ntibagiranwa" inyuma yo gutahukana igikombe ca Premier League kigira kane mu myaka y'inkino itanu
 City yatahukanye iri higanwa irushije inota rimwe gusa umukeba wayo Liverpool inyuma y'intsinzi ya 3-2 yaraye ironse mu gutsinda bigoranye Aston Villa ku musi wa nyuma w'ihiganwa ku kibuga Etihad Stadium
 Ni igikombe kigize 11 Guardiola atahukanye mu myaka itandatu kuva ashitse mu Bwongereza
 Guardiola ati: "Turi intibagiranwa
 Tuzokwama twibukwa
 Aba bakinyi bazokwama bibukwa muri uno murwi"
 "Ivyo twashitseko, ni ibintu bigoye cane
 Sir Alex Ferguson na Manchester United barabikoze, haraciye imyaka - incuro zibiri canke zitatu - ubu rero ndabonye ic'ari co gushika ku kintu nk'iki"
 Hasigaye iminota 15 gusa ngo urukino ruhere, City yari imaze guterwa 2-0 na Villa imbere y'uko Ilkay Gundogan yinjira agatera ibitsindo bibiri, hagati yavyo umukinyi wo hagati Rodri akaba yashoboye kwinjiza igitsindo, ibintu vyabaye mu minota itanu gusa itahukana intsinzi
 Iyo baramuka batsinzwe canke bakanganya gusa, Liverpool niyo iba yaraye mu munezero
 Guardiola  ati: "Urukino rwa nyuma igihe cose rwama ari urukino rudasanzwe - ibigumbagumba vyinshi
 Aston Villa ntaco batakoze, ariko igitsindo ca mbere cahinduye vyose
 Vyari ngombwa ko dufata ibintu mu minwe"
 "Iyo utsindiye iri higanwa incuro zine mu myaka itanu, ni uko aba bahungu ari ibitangaza
 "Gutsindira muhira imbere y'abantu bacu ni ikintu gihimbaye
 Igihe tumariye kunganya, twaciye twumva ko twari dufise amahirwe yo gutsinda ica gatatu
 "Ni bwo bwa mbere nari mbaye mu bihe nk'ibi kuva nagashika hano"
 Liverpool yatsinze umurwi wa Wloves 3-1 ku kibuga cayo ariko ntiyashoboye gutesha Manchester City gukingira igikombe cayo yari isanzwe ifise
 Mw'ihiganwa ryose rirangiye, iyi mirwi ibiri yatakarije inkino zitanu gusa, Citi zitatu, Liverpool zibiri
 Guardiola  yongerako ati: "Ivyo twaraye dushitseko bifitaniye isano n'ubukomezi bw'abakeba bacu kandi sinari bwigere mbona umurwi nka Liverpool mu buzima bwanje
 "Turakeje Liverpool - baratumye uko indwi yose irangiye tugenda tuvyifatamwo neza"
 Abajijwe nimba afise umugambi wo kubandanya amenyereza uyu murwi igihe amasezerano afitaniye nawo azoba arangiye mu mpera z'umwaka w'inkino uza, yavuze ati: "Nta shaka canke icipfuzo co kwiyumvira ivy'umwaka uza mfise muri kino gihe
 "Nta mwaka w'inkino woroshe
 Sinshobora guhemukira umurwi  - kumbure banshira mu bihe bidasanzwe mu buzima bwanje ariko ntegerezwa kuvyiyumvamwo, abakinyi bategerezwa kuvyiyumvamwo mbere n'umurwi utegerezwa kuvyiyumvamwo
 "Ubu ni igihe co kwidagadura
 Dusubiriye gutahukana ihiganwa"
 Umukinyi mpuzamakungu wa Ukraine, Oleksandr Zinchenko yinjiye mu gice ca kabiri aca ahindura ibintu muri Manchester City anagira uruhara rukomeye mu guhereza umupira Rodri agatera ica kabiri
 Yahimbaje iyi ntsinzi mu kibuga umupira  uheze afise ibendera ya Ukraine yari akenyeye mu bitugu, yifotoza ayambaye imbere yo kuyambika igikombe aca akorora amosozi
 Ati: "[Ibi] ni ibihe vy'ikigumbagumba ntibagiranwa kuri jewe - ku banya Ukraine bose bariko bicwa n'inzara, bari mu magorwa mu gihugu canje kubera igitero c'Uburusiya
 "Ndishimiye kuba umunya Ukraine no gutahukana iki gikombe muri Ukraine, kubw'abanya Ukraine bose kubera bagikwiye
 "Gisigura vyose kuri jewe - numva nopfira aba banyagihugu n'abadufashe mu mugongo
 Ivyo abanyagihugu bampaye n'ivyo bankoreye muri iki gihe - igihe kitoroshe mu buzima bwanje -  ndabishima cane kandi sinzokwigera ndavyibagira mu buzima bwanje bwose"
 'Ntuzokwama ubona amahiganwa mensi aryoshe' Uwahoze ari myugariro wa Arsenal Martin Keown avuga ko vyari kuba "biteye agahinda" iyo City ibura igikombe muri uno mwaka w'ihiganwa, mu gihe Liverpool imaze gutahukana ibikombe bibiri mu gihugu kandi ikaba yiteguriye gutana mu mitwe na Real Madrid mu rukino rwa nyuma rw''ihiganwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere iwabo (Champions League)
 Uwahoze ari umusatirizi w'Ubwongereza Alan Shearer nawe yongerako ati: "Twabonye umurwi udasanzwe, umwaka udasanzwe n'urukino rw'umupira w'amaguru rudasanzwe
 "Ivyo Pep Guardiola akoze muri Manchester City n'ivyo Jurgen Klopp akoze muri Liverpool ni ibintu bidasanzwe
 Wari umutaga uryoheye ijisho ku muntu ataho yegamiye
 "Nagumanye umutima uhagaze ariko ntaho nari mpagaze - Imana yonyene niyo izi ivyari mu mitwe y'abafana, kuko uwu ni umuhingamo wari uteye ubwoba
 Ibintu bidasanzwe"
 'Twasiganywe n'umurwi wa mbere kw'isi yose' Umumenyereza wa Liverpool Klopp avuga ko wabaye "umunezero" kuri we gukorana n'aba bakinyi gihe cose, ariko bari bakeneye " gushiramwo inguvu zisumbirije mu gice ca mbere c'ihiganwa" kugira ngo dushobore gutsinda City muri uru rugamba
 Hagati aho, avuga ko ivyo bashitseko bidasanzwe kandi ko bagumye baterana inkokora "n'umurwi wa mbere kw'isi" gushika ku musi wa nyuma
 Ati: "Aba bahungu bakinye ihiganwa ridasanzwe
 Ntibirangiriye ng'aha, ahubwo niko ihiganwa rirangiye"

Abantu imiriyoni zitanu barateshejwe izabo ubu bakaba ari impunzi zo hagati mu gihugu muri Ethiopia, nico gitigiri ca mbere kinini  c'abantu nkabo kizwi mu gihugu kimwe, nk'uko biri mu cegeranyo
 Ico cegeranyo  gikorwa buri mwaka n'ikigo gikurikirana ibijanye n'abateshejwe  izabo bagahungira mu gihugu hagati (Internal Displacement Monitoring Centre, IDMC), kivuga kandi ko Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo, Afghanistan na Myanmar (Birmanie) biri mu bihugu navyo vyagize abantu benshi bateshejwe izabo mu 2021
 Ico cegeranyo gisohotse mu gihe igitigiri ca mbere kinini ca miriyoni 59 z'abantu kw'isi yose baharuwe nk'abateshejwe izabo gushika mu mpera zo mu mwaka uheze kubera intambara zidahera hamwe n'imipfunda mishasha y'intureka
 Bivuze ko habaye ukwiyongera kwa miriyoni zine kw'isi yose ugereranije no mu mwaka uheze, nk'uko ico cegeranyo kibandanya kivuga
 Icegeranyo c'ico kigo cashinzwe n'ishirahamwe rya Norvège ryo gufasha impunzi (Norwegian Refugee Council), cerekana ko umugabane wa Afrika ariwo wa mbere ku bantu benshi bateshejwe izabo
 Mu buraruko bwa Ethiopia, intambara  imaze amezi 18 yarateye akaga gakomeye cane, aho abantu baharurwa muri za miriyoni bavanywe mu buzima bwabo bwa minsi yose
 Igitigiri nyaco c'abantu baguye muri iyo ntambara - yavuzwemwo amabi n'amahano amwe amashirahamwe y'agateka ka zina muntu avuga ko ashobora kuba ari ivyaha vyo mu ntambara - gushika ubu ntikizwi neza
 Mu ntara y'amajaruguru cane ya Tigray, aho intambara yatanguriye mu kwezi kwa Munyonyo (11)  mu 2020, abantu baharurwa muri za miriyoni n'ubu baracakeneye cane imfashanyo
 Mu bindi bice vy'igihugu, urugero rutari bwigere rushikwako rw'intureka ishingiye ku moko yatumye abantu ibihumbi n'ibihumbi bahunga ingo zabo
 Ubu ingabo za reta ziri mu gikorwa ca gisirikare co kurwanya umugwi witwaje ibigwanisho wo muri Oromia, intara ya mbere nini muri Ethiopia -wa Oromo Liberation Army (OLA) - hakaba hari impungenge ko gishobora kugwamwo abanyagihugu basanzwe no gutuma akaga karushiriza gukomera

Umukuru w'igihugu ca Ukraine Volodymyr Zelensky yagiriza Uburusiya ko bwahinduye akarere ka Donbas kari mu buseruko bukakagira "umuriro udahera", ni mu gihe intambara aho zibica bigacika
 Mw'ijambo yaraye ashikirije mw'ijoro ry'ejo ku mugwa mukuru Kyiv, yavuze ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zasambuye ako karere kose
 Ati: "Ibitero ni urutavanako mu karere ka Odesa, ku bisagara vyo hagati muri Ukraine
 Donbas yasambuwe rwose"
 Zelensky yongerako ati: "Uburusiya nta nsiguro ya gisirikare kandi ntayo bushobora kugira mu gukora ibi vyose"
 "Ubu ni ubukozi bw'ikibi bwo gushaka kwica n'ibigirankana abanyagihugu ba Ukraine benshi bashoboka
 Gusenyura imihana myinshi, inyubakwa n'amahinguriro menshi ashoboka"
 Ejo ku wa kane, umushikiranganji wa Ukraine ajejwe kwivuna abansi yagirije Uburusiya kwongereza ibitero muri Donbas no kubuza abasivire guhunga
 Uburusiya bwimuriye urugamba hafi rwose mu buseruko bwa Ukraine, inyuma y'aho bukuriye ingabo zabwo mu micungararo y'umugwa mukuru Kyiv
 Urugamba rw'aka karere ka Ukraine kahoze karwiriyemwo amahinguriro kazwi nka Donbas ishobora kwerekana iherezo ry'igitero c'Uburusiya
 Donbas irwiriyemwo abakoresha ururimi rw'ikirusiya kandi Abarusiya babandanya bavuga ko bashaka "kubohoza" aka karere karimwo intara zibiri ziherutse gutangaza ko ziyonkoye kuri Ukraine za Luhansk na Donestsk
 Kwigarurira aka karere bishobora gutuma Moscou ironka ikiraro c'ubutaka ku rubibe rw'Uburusiya ku ruhande rw'ubumanuko, maze igashobora kugenzura irungikwa ry'amazi mu karere ka Crimée/Crimea yigaruriye mu 2014
 Ingabo z'Uburusiya zariko kandi ziragerageza kugota ingabo za Ukraine muri ako karere
 Abasirikare ba Kyiv bakomeye kandi bamenyereye intambara bababa 40
000 bari muri Donbas, vyumvikana ko mu gihe Volodymry Zelensky yobatakaza coba ari ikibazo gikomeye kuri we muri ino ntambara
 Ariko muri iyi misi ya vuba iheze, abihweza ibintu n'ibindi mu vya gisirikare bavuga ko ibintu bitoroheye Uburusiya, kuko ingabo zabwo zirukanywe mu gisagara ca Kharkiv zigatera zija amaja ku rubibe rw'Uburusiya
 Ni mu gihe buramatari mushasha w'intara ya Kherson iri mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine iherutse gufatwa avuga ko vuba izokwegekwa ku Burusiya
 Volodymyr Saldo yashizweho n'ingabo z'Uburusiya inyuma yo kwigarurira ako karere mu ntango z'ukwa gatatu, yanditse ku rubuga rwa Telegram ko ishobora kuba "akarere ka Kherson kegukira Uburusiya"
 Icegera ciwe, Kirill Stremousov, yandika ko ababa muri ako karere bazoshobora gusaba ubwenegihugu bw'Uburusiya mu ndwi ziri imbere igihe ibintu bizoba bisubiye mu buryo
 Abategetsi ba Ukraine babandanya bagabisha ko Moscou itegura kamarampaka y'amanyanga yo kwemeza ukwikukira kw'ako karere n'ahandi
 Ariko, abategetsi b'Uburusiya ntibaremeza ko uturere buherutse kwigarurira mu bumanuko bwa Ukraine turi hafi yo kubwegekwako, mu gihe umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov mu ntango z'uku kwezi yavuze ko kazoza k'aka karere kazovana n'ugushaka kw'abakabamwo

