Umugabo w'umunya Ethiopia w'imyaka 69 afise abana 11 yavuzwe cane ku mbuga hwaniro mu gihugu ce inyuma yo kwiyandikisha kw'ishure kaminuza afise imyaka 69
 Tadesse Ghichile yaramaze imyaka myinshi atarashobora kurangiza amashure yisumbuye inyuma y'aho aburiye abavyeyi akiri muto amaze kurangiza amashure mato
 Ubu yatanguye kwiga kw'ishure kaminuza ya Jimma iri mu burengero bw'igihugu aho yizeye ko azoharonkera urupapuro rw'umutsindo mu vyo ubuvuzi
 Tadesse Ghichile ni umurimyi
 Iyo atari mu mirima yiwe, yisumamwo mu kaguriro k'ibifungurwa kugira ngo ashobore kuronka igitunga umuryango
 Ariko kandi, yashoboye kuronka akaryo ko gukora ikibazo - kandi aragitora - co kwinjira mw'ishure kaminuza
 Hari haciye imyaka cumi afashe ingingo yo gusubira kw'ishure yari yahagaritse ageze mu mwaka w'umunani inyuma y'aho abavyeyi biwe bapfiriye
 Yari amaze igihe kirekire arondera gusubira kw'ishure, ariko ntivyamworoheye na gato, cane cane amaze gushinga umuryango
 Ariko rero amaze kugaruka, yaciye yiyemeza kubandanya gushika ku kanyuma
 Ubu yinjiye rimwe mu mashure kaminuza makuru makuru mu gihugu
 Yabwiye BBC ko abanyeshure bagenziwe bamufashije cane mu myaka mike iheze kandi ko ubu yiteze kubona ibiri imbere

Kapiteni wa Gabon akaba n'umukinyi w'imbere wa Barcelona Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang yasezeye gukinira igihugu mu gihe himirije ihiganirwa  ryo gushika mu nkino za nyuma z'igikombe ca Afrika Can 2023
 Uwo mukinyi w'imyaka 32 yakiniye Les Pantheres incuro 68 yinjiza ibitsindo 29, bituma gushika ubu aba ari we mukinyi amaze kwinjiiriza ibitsindo vyinshi ico gihugu
 Mw'itangazo,  urwego rw'igihugu rujejwe umupira w'amaguru muri Gabon (Fegafoot) rwamenyesheje ko rwaronse ikete rya Aubameyang arumenyesha ingingo yiwe
 Yarwandikiye ati: " Inyuma y'imyaka 13  nserukira igihugu canje  , nashaka kubamenyesha ko mpagaritse gukinira igihugu
" "Nashaka gushimira abanya-Gabon bose n'abandi bose banshingikiye mu bihe vyiza na bibi
 "Nzokwama  nibuka ibihe bikomeye nk'igihe nakinira igihugu ubwa mbere, canke igihe nataha mvuye muri Nigeria ntahukanye agashimwe k'umukinyi w'umunya-Afrika w'umwaka
 Kugasangira n'abandi bose n'igihe ntibagirwa
 "Nshaka gushimira data we yashatse ko nomera nka we   kandi nizigiye ko namushimishije mu kwambara umwambaro w'igijhugu cacu
" Mu kumwishura, Fegafoot yemeye  "akazi keza yakoze" no kuba umukinyi "yari azi ingene ateza imbere, kubera ubunyamwuga bwiwe, ishusho ya Gabon mu makungu"
 "Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang azokwama ari intangarugero ku bariko bararuka," nk'uko Fegafoot yongeyeko
 "Umuryango wagutse w'umupira w'amaguru uzoguma uzeye vyinshi ku buhinga bwiwe muri kazoza
" Aubameyang  yavukiye mu Bufaransa hanyuma akinira ico gihugu mu rugero rw'abafise munsi y'imyaka 21 ariko aca arahindura akinira Gabon kugira agendere mu makanda ya se, yabaye kapiteni igihe Gabon yashika ubwa mbere mu nkino za nyuma z'igikombe ca Afrika mu 1994
 Ntiyamye afitaniye imigenderanire myiza na Fagafoot, aho nko mu 2018 yanegura urwo rwego igihe rwatangaza ko se wiwe yari agiye kuba umumenyereza mushasha w'umugwi nserukiragihugu mu gihe amasezerano yavyo atari bwaherahezwe
 Aubameyang  yatanguye gukinira Gabon  mu rukino batsinzemwo Maroc mu 2009, hanyuma akinira igihugu ciwe mu nkino zine za nyuma z'igikombe ca Afrika
 Uwo mukinyi w'imbere yari ku rutonde rw'abakiniye Gabon mw'ihiganwa c'igikombe ca Afrika ca 2021 ariko cakiniwe gitevye ariko nta rukino na rumwe yakinye inyuma y'aho mu ntango yanduriye Covid-19 mu nyuma akarwara icavuzwe ico gihe ko twari 'udukomere ku mutima'
 Les Pantheres bazotangura inkino zo gukuranamwo z'igikombe ca Afrika ca 2023 muri Cote d'Ivoire aho bazokina na Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo itariki zine za Ruheshi (6)  hanyuma ikine urukino rwa kabiri rwo mu mirwi na Mauritania ku wa 8 Ruheshi

