 Yongeyeko:"Rurangiranwa mu mupira w'amaguru, ku musi wa gatandatu  bari ku kibuga baranerekana ishaka ryo kugwanya ikumirwa ry'abafitaniye ubucuti bushingiye ku gitsina bagisangiye hamwe n'irindi kumira iryo ari ryo ryose
" Inyifato ya Gueye yarashigikiwe n'ibihangange muri politike mu gihugu ca Senegal
 Prezida w'ico gihugu Macky Sall yanditse kuri Twitter ko ukwemera kwa Gueye nk'umu Islam gutegerezwa kwubahirizwa, mu gihe umushikiranganji wo kwinonora imitsi na we Matar Ba yanditse ko Gueye ashigikiwe n'abanye Senegal aho yashizeko ifoto y'uyo mukinyi wo hagati ari mu rugendo rweranda ima Maka

