 Uyu mukinyi wo hagati ku ruhande rw'inyuma abona ko umurwi wiwe wananiwe no guhangana n'ibihe bitoroshe mu rugamba rwo kurondera kuba muri ine ya mbere mw'ihiganwa ryo mu Bwongereza
 Iyo iramuka itsinze yari kuja imbere ya Tottenham, gutyo ikabandanya ifise amahirwe yo kuronka ikibanza mw'ihiganwa rihuza imirwi yabaye iya mbere i Bulaya (Ligue des Champions/Champions League)  mu gihe hasigaye urukino rumwe
 Ati: "Iyo umuntu yumva afise ubwoba mu rukino nk'uru, guma muhira
 "Nta kuraba imyaka
 Iyo wumva ufise ubwoba, guma hanze canke ugume muhira
 Hakenewe abantu baza ngaha biteguye gukina
 Rwari rumwe mu nkino nyamukuru kuri twebwe
 Twumva ducitse intege ku bantu baje ngaha"
 Hagati aho, mu kiganiro n'imboneshakure y'inkino Sky Sports, uwahoze akina inyuma muri  Manchester United Gary Neville aranegura amajambo ya  Xhaka
 Ati: "Yama ashwanira abakinyi mu cumba co kwihinduriramwo
 "Nibaza ko atari akwiye kunegura aba bakinyi bakiri bato kuko na we nyene yagiye abateza urubwa kenshi, ahabwa amakarata atukura n'ibindi
 Aho yarabashize mu ngorane"
 Kugira ngo Arsenal igire amahirwe yo kuja muri zine za mbere, itegerezwa gutsinda umurwi wa Everton ku kibuga cayo ku wa Mungu hanyuma Tottenham nayo -  iyisumvya amanota abiri ikanayirusha n'ibitsindo vyinshi - itsindwe na Norwich yamaze kumanuka mu cicaro ca kabiri
 Xhaka yabwiye BBC Sport ati: "Twashaka gukina urukino rwiza ariko vyanse
 "Abantu bama bata ishavu ku burongozi
 Ntituriko dukina tennis, turiko dukina umupira w'amaguru
 Iyo umuntu yumva afise ubwoba mu bihe bigoye nk'ibi, guma muhira
 "Ntushobora kuza ngaha hanyuma ngo ukine nk'uku
 Twakinye nabi cane uno musi
 Integuro zacu twari dufise ziratandukanye  rwose n'ingene twakinye
 Twakinye urukino atari rwo na gatoya
 "Batunesheje kuva ku munota wa mbere gushika ku wa 96
 Ukina gutya, ntukwiye kuja muri Champions League
 "Ikibazo ni uko turi mu bihe bigoye
 Iyo udashoboye kwifata neza mu bihe bigoye, ibintu birangira nk'uko vyarangiye uno musi
 Biboneka ko ata kintu dushoboye iyo turi mu bihe bigoye"
 Igitsindo Ben White yitsinze mu minota ya mbere y'igice ca kabiri c'uru rukino catumye Newcastle irusha Arsenal imbere y'uko Bruno Guimaraes atera ica kabiri mu minota ya nyuma
 Xhaka yongerako ati: "Mu gihe Tottenham yotsindwa natwe tugatsinda, ivy'umupira ni akananirabahinga"
 "Ni ngombwa ko twizera
 Imbere y'urukino, ibintu vyose twari tubifise mu minwe
 Twakinye urukino rutari rwo na gato"
 Uru rukino rwabaye urwa gatandatu Arsenal itsinzwe mu nkino 11 za Premier League  - hakaba hari haciye imisi ine itsinzwe 3-0 na Tottenham - mbere n'umumenyereza Mikel Arteta akaba yemera ko Newcastle yarushije umurwi wiwe mu bice vyose
 Ati: "Ni ibintu bitoroshe kwemera, ariko nta nkeka Newcastle yari ikwiriye iyi ntsinzi mu buryo bwose
 "Vyari ngombwa ko duhangana n'aya majoro [harimwo n'iryo twatsinzwe na Tottenham] ariko vyanse
 "Newcastle badusumbije incuro 100 zose
  Mu bice vyose, utegerezwa kuvyifatamwo neza, ariko ntavyo twashoboye
 "Dutegerezwa kwigora tukemera ko umukino wacu ataho uhuriye na gato n'uwa Champions League
 "Nacitse inguvu bidasanzwe
 Ni ikintu kibabaje cane
 Ibintu vyari mu minwe yacu uno musi ariko vyaducitse
 Ni ngombwa ko dutsinda Everton hanyuma tukarindira ko Norwich yotsinda Spurs
 Igihe cose hama hari amahirwe matoya mu mupira w'amaguru
 "Kuva ku wa kabiri, tuzoba turiko twitegurira Everton
 Vyose birashoboka mu biharuro"
 Newcastle yagiye ivyifatamwo neza kuva igihe iguriye abakinyi bashasha mu kwa mbere, ariko kandi n'umumenyereza wayo Eddie Howe yarahinduye abakinyi batari bake yasanzeho

Umugwi ndangakaranga w'abatimbo b'u Burundi wo mu Gishora (Gitega) uvuga ko wishuza leta amafaranga miliyoni 12 wakoresheje mu myiteguro y'urugendo rwo  guherekeza umukuru w'igihugu
 Uwo mugwi wa Gishora niwo wari watoranijwe ngo uherekeze Prezida Evariste Ndayishimiye mw'isabukuru ryabereye i Dubai (Dubai Expo 2020) ryatanguye mu kwezi kwa Gitugutu 2021, uca ukurwa muri urwo rugendo ku munota wa nyuma
 Aho mu Gishobora, niho hasanzwe hari  umuzi w'umuco wo kuvuza ingoma z'u Burundi, umuco w'ubuhinga bivugwa ko ushobora kuba umaze imyaka amajana
 Mu kwitegurira urwo rugendo, uwo mugwi uvuga ko wakoresheje amafaranga menshi mu gufata ingendo baja i Bujumbura kurondera impapuro za nkenerwa, kuriha aho barara hamwe n'ivyo bafungura
 Abo batimbo ba Gishora bavuga ko ico bobo bakeneye ari gushumbushwa ivyo bakoresheje bitegurira urugendo rwaje kujamwo abandi ku munota wanyuma kandi ku buryo butumvikana
 Bavuga yuko ikibazo cabo cakomeje guteragiranwa n'ubushikiranganji butandukanye
 Florentine Kwizera yavuganye n'umuyobozi wabo, Pacifique Nshimirimana, atangura amusigurira uko ico kibazo giteye (urashobora kwumva ico kiganiro aho hejuru)
 Ibi ni ibindi woraba:
Prezida mushasha wa Somalia, Hassan Sheikh Mohamud, si mushasha muri ayo mabanga
 Yabaye umukuru wa Somalia agira uwa munani kuva mu 2012 gushika mu 2017 aca atsindwa amatora yo mu 2017 n'uwahora ari umukuru w'igihugu Mohamed Abdullahi "Farmajo"
 Yongeye kwandika amateka ku wa mungu mu gutorwa irigira kabiri mw'ihiganwa rya mbere rikomeye cane muri kahise k'ico gihugu, amatora yashitse ku ncuro ya gatatu
 Ukwiyamamaza kw'uwo yahoze aharanira kugarukana amahoro kwari gushingiye ku gusubiza abanya -Somalia hamwe  no kubana mu mahoro n'amakungu - ikintu atibagiwe kugarukako buno nyene agiheza kurahirira amabanga ku wa mbere mu gitondo
 Yavuze ati: "Ndabemereye ko tuzokorana cane n'ibihugu bibanyi hamwe n'abo dusanzwe dufashanya mu makungu
" Mw'ijwi yumvikana nk'umuntu ashaka gusubiza hamwe kandi yemerera abanya-Somalia ko azokorera bose
 Amaherezo yatahukanye ubwiganze bw'amajwi menshi muri ayo matora yabaye mu ncuro zitatu, aho yaronse amajwi 214,  uwo bahiganwa Farmajo akaronka 110, gutyo aca yihora uwari yamurushije mu 2017
 Mohamud yari amaze imyaka ibiri iheze  ahanini aba i Mogadishu, aguma yamamaza ko amatora yoba ku gihe kandi nk'uko vyemewe
 Yari umwe  mu runani rw'aba-kandida batavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi bari bateye kubiri n'ingendo ya prezida Farmajo yo kurondera kwongera imyaka ibiri ku kiringo ciwe
 Mu kwezi kwa kabiri mu 2021, abajejwe umutekano barateye ihoteri yabamwo i Mogadishu kugira bahagarike imyiyerekano abatavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi bashaka kugira ku murwa mukuru
 Ari mu bategetsi bake bagumye muri Somalia mu myaka 30 ico gihugu kimaze mu ntambara yo mu gihugu hagati
 Uwo agiye kuba umukuru wa Somalia atoranye igihugu gihanzwe na vyinshi, harimwo n'uruzuba rukaze cane ONU ivuga ko rushobora gutera inzara hamwe atacokorwa
 Abantu bashika miriyoni 3
5 bakeneye imfashanyo y'ivyo kurya yihuta kandi barashobora kwicwa n'inzara
 Azotegerezwa guhangana kandi n'ubuzima buguma buzimba hamwe n'ibiciro biguma vyiyongera vyaje gusongwa  n'ingwano yo muri Ukraine
 Urundi rugamba rumurindiriye n'ingene  intara  zikomeza kutiyumva mu butegetsi mpuzantara, ico kibazo kikaba cagumye mu vyari bihanze ubutegetsi bwahahora
 Ni ikibazo asanzwe ashobora gutorera inyishu mu gihe zimwe muri izo ntara ari we yazishinze igihe yatwara ikiringo ca mbere
 Abasesenguzi bavuga ko azotegerezwa gusanura imigenderanire n'ibihugu nka Kenya, Djibouti na Reta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu (UAE)
 Ubutetegetsi bwahahora bwarahagaritse imigenderanire na Kenya  ku ncuro zitandukanye  kandi baragiraniye amatati afatiye ku rubibe rwo mu mazi
 Mu 2012, yatumye Somalia yongera kugira imigenderanire inyuma y'ama reta y'imfatakibanza, aca asubira kwunga imigenderanire n'ibihugu vya Buraya hamwe n'ivyo muri Afrika
 Ariko yaraneguwe cane mu kunanirwa gutorera inyishu ibiturire vyavugwa mu butegetsi bwiwe
 Uwo mugabo yavukiye muri Hiran yo hagati mu 1955
 Yakuriye mu kibano cifashe muri Mogadishu aca atsinda amashure kuri kaminuza y'igihugu ya Somalia mu gisata c'ubuhinga mu 1981
 Abo bakuranye bavuga ko yari umuntu avuga make kandi yicisha bugufi aca aba umwigisha imbere y'uko aja kubandanya amashure kuri kaminuza ya Bhopal mu Buhindi
 Agarutse yaciye aja mu bushikiranganji bw'indero aho yashinzwe umugambi w'inderabigisha ku buryo bwa ONU
 Igihe reta mpuzantara yatembagara mu 1991, yaciye aja gukora muri Unicef  ajejwe gukurikirana inyigisho, agendera intara zo hagati n'ubumanuko bwa Somalia, ingendo zamufashije kubona "ingene igisata y'amashure cariko kiratabagara
" Inyuma y'imyaka itatu yaciye ashinga rimwe mu mashure ya mbere y'intango i Mogadishu kuva intambara yaduka
 Afitaniye isano na al-Islah, ishami rya Somalia rya Muslim Brotherhood, ryafashije cane  mu gusubira kuvyura ibijanye n'amashure muri ico gihe c'intambara
 Barubutse amashure menshi ashingiye kuri Islam nk'ayo usanga muri Sudan na Misiri ariko akaba ateye kubiri  cane n'umugwi wa jihad al-Shabab  ubu ushamikiye kuri al-Qaeda
 Umugabo avugwa kuba umu-Islamist  yoroheje mu gihugu ciganjemwo aba-Islam hafi cose,  Mohamud avugwa kandi ko yigeze kuba afise imigenderanire na Union of Islamist Courts  (UIC),  urufatane rw'ama sentare  mu ntango rwashinzwe n'abagwizatunga kugirango barabe ko bazana amategeko muri ico gihugu kitarangwamwo amategeko inyuma y'imyaka myinshi y'ingwano
 UIC zarazanye agahengwe k'amahoro mu gihugu mu 2016, imbere y'uko Ethiopia itera ikazisambura - itewe ubwoba n'uko al-Shabab yariko irazigarurira buke buke
 Abamuyoboka bavuga ko mu nyuma yashigikiye igikorwa cose coza kigarukama amahoro n'amaragano
 Mu myaka ya 1990, Mohamud yaragize uruhara rukomeye mu mashirahamwe adaharanira inyungu za poritike, kandi abantu bamuzi bavuga ko yafashije cane mu gutatura amatati yo mu miryango (clans)
 Ica mbere yashitseko gikomeye muri iyo nzira kwabaye ukwitaba ibiganiro vyo mu 1997 vyavanyeho icari kizwi nka "Green Line", umurongo wagaburamwo Mogadishu kabiri hagati y'abakuru b'imiryango
 Uwo murongo wavugwa na bamwe mu myaka ya 1990 nka "cancer ya  Mogadishu "  watuma ubuzima bugorana cane ku baba muri ico gisagara co kimwe no ku banya-poritike
 Mu 2001, yagiye gukora mu kigo c'ubushashakatsi n'ibiganiro (Centre for Research and Dialogue)  nk'umushakashatsi mu gusanura ibihugu bivuye mu ntambara - ikigo  gikunze kunegurwa ko cegamiye cane ibihugu vya Buraya - yaranakoze cane nk'umuhinga w'inzego zitandukanye za ONU mu gihe ca reta mfatakibanza
 Ivyo bikorwa nta nkeka ko bizomufasha mu gihe azoba ariko aragerageza kuvana Somalia mu myaka 30 y'ingwano y'urutavanako

Urubanza rudasanzwe ruriko ruravugwa cane mu Buhindi
 Umugabo n'umugore bitwariye umuhungu wabo n'umugore wiwe kubera batarabavyarira umwuzukuru inyuma y'imyaka itandatu bubakanye
 Sanjeev na Sadhana Prasad, b'imyaka 61 na 57, bavuga ko bakoresheje uburyo bwabo bwose mu kurera umuhungu wabo, bamurihira ivyigwa vyo kugendesha indege, ubugeni buteye igomwe na ka karuhuko k'ubugeni (lune de miel/honeymoon)
 Ubu rero bavuga ko hageze ko abishura - umuhungu wabo canke umukazana bategerezwa kubavyarira umwuzukuru mu kiringo c'umwaka umwe gusa canke naho babashumbushe n'amafaranga angana n'imiriyoni 50 z' amarupiya (roupies/rupees, amafaranga akoreshwa mu Buhindi), ni ukuvuga 650
000 y'amadorari y'abanyamerika
 N'aho uyu muryango mushasha utaragira ico uvuze kuri ibi, urwandiko bandikiye sentare rurerekana ko imigenderanire hagati y'umuryango wa Prasad n'uw'umuhungu wabo atari myiza
 Avugana na BBC Hindi, Sadhana Prasad avuga ko kubona umuhungu wiwe n'umukazana baranse kuvyara abana vyabazaniye "uruvugo mu babanyi" akavuga ko ari "ubugome bwo mu mutwe"
 Nyina w'uyu muhungu ati: "Nta kundi twogira atari ukwitura ubutungane
 Twaragerageje kuganira nabo ariko igihe cose tuzanye ikibazo c'abuzukuru, baca bagerageza kugikwepa
 Ingingo yabo yo kutavyara isigura ko izina ry'umuryango wacu rishobora kuzimangana"
 Umugabo wiwe nawe ati: "Turababaye cane
 Turashaje
 Dushaka kuba ba sekuru na inakuru
 Mbere turipfuza no kubarerera abana
 Abuzukuru bazana umunezero ku bantu, ariko twebwe uwu munezero ntawo dufise"
 Urubanza rw'abavyeyi bashengeza abana babo muri sentare kubera batabavyariye abuzukuru kumbure rufise kuba ari akataraboneka, ariko nk'uko benshi bashobora kubivuga, kuvyara umwana ni nk'uko atari ingingo ifatwa ku gushaka kw'abubakanye
 Bose - kuva ku bavyeyi, ba sebukwe na inabukwe gushika mu miryango ya hafi n'iyakure eka mbere no mu babanyi - barafisemwo ijambo, kandi imiryango itangura kubatira kuvyara hakiri kare bataranamenyera n'urugo
 Umuhinga mu vy'imibereho y'abantu Prof AR Vasavi asigura ati: "Mu Buhindi, kurongorana ni hagati y'imiryango, ntabwo ari abareshanya bonyene"
 Ivyo umuryango wa Prasad usaba "vyo kuronka abuzukuru bishingiye n'imico n'imigenzo"
 "Bafata ko ari uburenganzira bwabo bwo kuronka abuzukuru kuko mu karanga kacu kwubaka bifatwa nk'ikigo gihezagira iryara, rero iyo uramutse wubatse uba witezwe ko uvyarira urugo, umuryango, n'ababanyi
 "Barafatira kandi ku mpamzu zishingiye ku butunzi kuko nimba narakoresheje amafaranga kukurihira amashure no kukurera, ni ngombwa ko wubahiriza ivyo usabwa n'imico n'imigenzo, ubishaka canke utabishaka"
 Iki kibazo c'uko abana bategerezwa kuvyarira abavyeyi babo abuzukuru ni ikintu kiri hose, ntikiraba ngo ni umuryango nyabaki, idini nyabaki, ntikiraba ngo uba mu gisagara canke mu misozi
 Umunyamakuru Ritu Agarwal avuga ko mu 2019, umuhindi wa mbere atunze kurusha abandi bose - Mukesh Ambani - yavuzwe cane mu binyamakuru igihe "yumvikana abwira" umukazana wiwe mushasha Shloka ko hari hageze y'uko amuvyarira samuragwa
 "Ndazi ko, igihe nzoba ndakwipfuriza umwaka uza mushasha, uretse ko nzoba ndi sekuru, nawe uzoba uri nyina w'abana", niko yumvikanye avuga ajajura muri videwo yasohowe n'umuryango igihe bamugirira umusi mukuru w'amavuko
 Mu kiringo kiri musi y'amezi 18 inyuma y'aho, nk'uko umupfasoni Agarwal abivuga, Shloka yari yavyaye umwana w'umuhungu
 Mu Buhindi, Sentare nkuru y'igihugu yaremeje ko "imico n'amategeko" bitegeka ko umuhungu afasha abavyeyi biwe iyo bageze mu zabukuru, ariko abaharanira agateka ka muntu bavuga ko kuvyara umwana canke kutavyara ari ingingo itegerezwa gufatwa n'umugore
 Ariko abagore benshi barongowe bavuga ko aka gahato  ko kuryara baterwa mu muryango no mu kibano kabashira mu ngorane zidakenewe
 Sudha (izina ryahinduwe), umuhinga w'imyaka 46 yihweza ibintu n'ibindi aba mu gisagara ca Bangalore kiri mu bumanuko bw'igihugu, yabwiye BBC ko igihe abavyeyi bamurongoza, yari afise imyaka 21 kandi ko ari ho yari agiheza amashure
 "Iyo turi mu misi mikuru, abanyamuryango b'umugabo wanje baguma bambaza ngo 'ni ryari uzoduha inkuru nziza?' Jewe nari nkiri muto kandi sinashobora kumenya ico ndabishura
 Ariko vyari ibintu biteye akoba kandi igihe cose bama babimbaza, narumva ko ntorohewe"
 Aho haraciye imyaka 25 kandi, nk'uko abivuga, abagore hafi bose baba bahanzwe amaso n'imiryango ku buryo mu mwaka wa mbere canke wa kabiri kuva barongowe baba bamaze kuryara
 "Ariko ico mbona ni uko, gushika n'ubu, abagore bose, cane cane mu bisagara bito bito no mu mitumba, bategerezwa kubigendera kandi ko bategerezwa kwihutira kuvyara umwana vuba bishoboka"
 Avuga ko uru rubanza "rubabaje", ariko igitsure co kuvyara umwana kirabandanya
 Ni ko kandi vyagenze no kuri muvyarawe Srishti (izina ryahinduwe kugira ntamenyekane) w'imyaka 28, avuga ko amaze amezi 17 yubatse, abatama bari bamaze kumubwira "incuro indwi canke umunani" ko "hageze kuvyara umwana"
 Sebukwe na inabukwe batanguye kuzana iki kibazo haciye amezi atandatu gusa arongowe
 Ariko we n'umugabo wiwe w'imyaka 30 akora mu gisata c'ubuhinga bwa none barongoranye ku mwumvikano w'abavyeyi, ntibakeneye kwihuta kuvyara umwana
 Ati: "Dukeneye kubanza kumenyana neza, tugakomeza umubano wacu hanyuma tukabanza kwitaho ubuzi bwacu ubu
 Kuvyara umwana ni umugambi wo kwitondera
 "Kandi numva ko abubakanye atari ngombwa ko bavyara mu gihe bataravyiyumvamwo ku mutima no bwenge kandi babona ko koko biteguriye kurera neza umwana bakamuronsa ivya nkenerwa vyose akenera"
 Avuga ko incuro nyinshi mu misi ya mbere "babajijwe ibijanye no kuvyara, twarasiguye igituma tutashaka kwihuta", ariko ico kibazo cagumye kigaruka
 Ati: "Bavuga ngo, 'oh, naka na naka bafise umwana
 Canke ngo uyu mukobwa canke urya mukobwa aherutse kurongorwa yaramaze kuronka umwana'
 Numva ari ukungora iyo babandanya bazana ico kibazo
 Ariko nirabira hasi nkabigwiza n'ubusa"

Abantu cumi muri Reta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bishwe barashwe mu ntara ya New York mu gitero kiriko gikorwako amatohoza ko coba gifatiye ku macakubiri y'urukoba
 Umusore w'imyaka 18 yari yambaye impuzu za gisirikare yahagaritswe inyuma y'uruhagarara rwabaye ahabereye iri bara mu gisagara ca  Buffalo
 Uwikekwa ko yakoze aka kabi yinjiye akaguriro karimwo abantu benshi nijoro ku wa gatandatu yugurura umuriro
 Igipolisi kivuga ko yanakoresheje na kamera mu kwerekana  ikibiriraho ico gitero yariko arakora
 Umukuru w'ico gihugu Joe Biden aramirira kure ico yita "akabi kabishe"
 Stephen Belongi, umukuru w'ibiro vya FBI mu gisagara ca Buffalo, yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Turiko turakora amatohoza ku vyabaye ko ari icaha gishingiye ku rwanko canke ko cakozwe n'intagondwa yitwaza amacakubiri y'urukoba"
 Uwufatwa ko yakoze aka kabi azwi ko yamaze amasaha atari make mu rugendo rwamushikanye muri aka karere karwiriyemwo abirabure
 Abantu cumi na batatu bose hamwe nibo barashwe kandi benshi muri bo ni abirabure, nk'uko bivugwa na Joseph Gramaglia, umukuru w'igipolisi i Buffalo
 Avugaka n'ikinyamakuru CBS, umupolisi avuga ko uyo mugabo yakoma induru avuga amajambo y'ibitutsi bishingiye ku rukoba igihe yariko akora ico gitero
 Gramaglia  yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Yururutse imodoka
 Yari afise ikigwanisho gikomeye
 Yari yambaye nk'umurwanyi
 Yari yambaye n'inkofero yo mu ntambara
 Yari afise kamera yariko akoresha mu kwerekana ikibiriraho ivyo yariko arakora"
 Avuga ko nyene gukora ivyo yashikirije ikirwanisho ciwe habanje kuba uguhangana gukomeye hanyuma aca atwarwa mu gasho
 Abo batatu bakomeretse - bose abakozi bo muri ako kaguriro - amagara yabo ntabangamiwe
 Umupolisi w'umukukuruke yari acunze ako kaguriro yagerageje kurasa uyo musore ariko na we nyene yabaye muri abo bantu bishwe, nk'uko igipolisi kibivuga
 Uyo musore amaze kwagirizwa icaha c'ubwicanyi bwo ku rugero rwa mbere, kandi umushikirizamanza w'akarere ka Erie, John Flynn, avuga ko hari ibindi vyaha bishobora kumwagira
 Umukuru w'akarere ka Buffalo, Byron Brown, yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Aka ni akaga kabi cane gashobora gushikira abanyagihugu kandi turababaye, ubu imitima iravyimvye"
 Yongerako ati: "Ntidushobora kwemera ko uyu muntu agengwa n'urwanko acanishamwo akarere kacu canke igihugu cacu"
 Grady Lewis, yabonye ico gitero ari mw'ibarabara, yabwiye abanyamakuru ko yabonye uyo mugabo yugurura umuriro
 "Nabonye uyo musore yinjira, nk'umusirikare, arunama aca atangura kurasa abantu"
 Shonnell Harris yariko akora muri ako kaguriro igihe ico gitero caba, yabwiye ikinyamakuru Buffalo News ko yumvise amasasu arenga 70 yarashwe mu gihe yariko agerageza guhunga aciye mu muryango w'inyuma
 Uyu mugore ati: "Akaguriro kari kuzuye abantu
 Hari muri weekend
 Kari agahomerabunwa"
 Avuga ivyakurikiye, umupolisi umwe yabwiye  Buffalo News ati: "Umengo uriko urorera ireresi iteye ubwoba, ariko si ireresi, ni ibintu vyabaye"
 Mu masaha yitereye y'ejo ku wa gatandatu, buramatari wa New York, Kathy Hochul yavuze ko uwufatwa ko ari we "yakoze iki gitero c'iterabwoba ni umuzungu agendera ku vyiyumviro vy'uko abazungu ari bo basumba bose (white supremacist)"
 Iki ni "igitero gisa n'ica gisirikare co gutera abantu basanzwe bariko barasuma mw'iduka", nk'uko yabivuze igihe yagendera igisagara ca Buffalo
 Mw'itangazo yasohoye, Perezida Joe Biden yavuze ko we n'umugore wiwe bariko barasengera abaguye muri ico gitero n'imiryango yabo
 Ati: "Urwanko rushingiye ku macakubiri y'urukoba ni akabi kabishe ku gihugu cacu
