Adidas yabujijwe gusubira gukoresha amasanamu yerekana amabere ari hejuru mu bikorwa vyayo vyo kwamamaza kuko yerekana ubwambure bweruye
 Amasanamu y'amabere y'abagore baharurwa muri mirongo b'amabara y'uruhu atandukanye, ubumere n'ubunini butandukanye batonze ku murongo yerekanywe ku rubuga rwa Twitter no ku vyapa bibiri
 Ikigo kijejwe ivyerekeye ukwamamaza, Advertising Standards Agency (ASA), casanze uburyo bwose butatu bukoreshwa bushobora gutera agasuzuguro
 Adidas yoyo ivuga ko kwamamaza muri ubu buryo "vyerekana ingene amabere ari kwinshi", bityo rero bikerekana ingene ari nkenerwa kwambara agapfukamabere mu kwinonora kameze neza
 Umuvugizi wa Adidas ishami ryo mu Bwongereza avuga ko iyi kompanyi ataco yiyagiriza ku butumwa buri muri iryo yamamaza rikiri ahabona ku rubuga rwayo ngurukanabumenyi
 Ubwo butumwa bwo kuri Twitter bwasohowe muri Ruhuhuma (2) bufise amajambo ngo: "Turemera ko amabere y'abagore uko aba ameze kwose n'uko angana kwose ari ngombwa ko acigatirwa neza
 "Ari co gituma udupfukamabere twacu dushasha two kwinonora tugizwe n'ubwoko 43, kugira ngo umwe umwe wese yihitiremwo ako bakwiranye"
 Ivyapa vyompi vyerekana amashusho asa y'abagore yakaswe, bikavuga biti: "Ni co gituma tutakoze ubwoko bumwe gusa bw'agapfukamabere k'inkino ngororamubiri"
 Iki kigo kijejwe ivyerekeye kwamamaza caronse abantu 24 bacituye bavuga ko kwamamaza hakoreshejwe abantu bambaye ubusa ata nsiguro bifise kandi bitesha agaciro abagore mu kubagira ibikoresho vyo kwinezereza mu buryo bwo guhuza ibitsina hamwe "no kubanganisha n'ibihimba vy'umubiri"
 Hari bamwe bacituye bakibaza nimba ibi vyapa bibereye gushirwa ahantu habona, aho abana bashobora kubabona
 Twitter nayo nyene ivuga ko ubwo butumwa bwaneguwe na bamwe bu bakoresha uru rubuga ariko ko bwahavuye buboneka ko budateye kubiri n'ametegeko ngenderwako
 Ikigo ASA kivuga ko kitibajije nimba ingene abo bagore berekanywe muri ubwo butumwa bwa Twitter bubagaragaza mu bwambure bwabo canke bukabafata nk'ibikoresho vyo kwinezereza
 Ariko cahavuye gisanga ubu butumwa bushobora gufatwa ko bwerekana ubwambure bwabo kandi bugasaba kwitonderwa kugira ngo ntihagire uwo butirimutsa
 Cafashe ingingo ko ivyo vyapa bitabereye gukoreshwa mu bibanza bitizwe neza aho bishobora kubonwa n'abana
  Adidas ishami ryo mu Bwongereza ivuga ko aya masanamu yari afise intumbero yo "kwerekana no kwishimira imforo n'ibihagararo bitandukanye, kwerekana ubudasa no kwerekana ingene gukora udupfukamabere dufata neza ufatiye ku kuntu umuntu angana ari nkenerwa"
 Kivuga ko aya masanamu yakaswe kugira ngo ntibamenyekane no mu ntumbero yo kubungabunga umutekano wabo, kikongerako y'uko abo bose berekanywe muri iri yamamaza babikoze ku gushaka kwabo kandi ko bashigikiye intumbero yayo

Ingabo za Ukraine mu gisagara kigira kabiri c'iki gihugu zasubije inyuma Aburusiya ku buryo vya muzinga vyabwo bidashobora kuzishikira, nk'uko umunyamakuru wa BBC uriyo abivuga
 Muri iyi ntambara, ingabo z'Uburusiya zari zimaze imisi 70 yose zicucagira Kharkiv amabombe y'urutavanako, mu gihe zoba zasubijwe inyuma iki gisagara coba cinjiye mu gahengwe
 Agace ka nyuma kabohowe ni ikigwati ca Pytomnyk, nk'uko vyaraye bitangajwe n'igisirikare ca Ukraine
 Hagati aho, ingabo z'Uburusiya ntiziriko zirasubira inyuma - nk'uko vyagenze mu micungararo ya Kyiv
 Zivugwa ko ziriko ziriyegeranya, aho ingabo zirwanira ku butaka ziva mu mabatayo (bataillons) atari make ziriko zirahamvya abandi
 Nayo mu ntara ya Donbas, igisirikare ca Ukraine congeye gutangaza ko casambuye ibiraro vyakoreshwa n'ingabo z'Uburusiya mu kujabuka uruzi ruri mu karere ka Luhansk mu buseruko bw'igihugu ahamaze imisi habera intambara zikomeye
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi wa Ukraine yasohoye amasanamu avugwa ko ari ibifaru vy'Uburusiya n'ibindi bimodoka vyasambuwe mu kigwati ca Bilohorivka, hafi y'igisagara ca Lysychansk kiri mu minwe ya reta ya Ukraine
 Umukuru w'akarere ka Luhansk Serhiy Haidai avuga ko Bilohorivka ari "ikirindiro ntamenwa" cari "gihanganye n'igitigiri kinini" c'ingabo z'Uburusiya - nk'uko bimeze i Mariupol
 Igisirikare c'Uburusiya ntaco kiravuga kuri ibi bivugwa na Ukraine, bitaremezwa n'uruhande rwigenga
 Inyuma y'aho bunaniriwe no gufata umugwa mukuru wa Ukraine, Kyiv, mu buraruko bushira ubuseruko bw'igihugu mu  ndwi za mbere z'iyi ntambara, Uburusiya bwavuze ko bugiye gushira inguvu zose mu buseruko kugira bwigarurire uturere twa Luhansk hamwe na Donetsk
 Gushika ubu, Moscou ntirashobora gushika kuri iyi ntumbero
 Umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi w'Ubwongereza Ben Wallace avuga ko Uburusiya buzova muri iyi ntambara muri Ukraine bwatakaje inguvu ugereranije n'aho bwari bugeze imbere y'igitero cabwo
 Avugana n'abanyamakuru i Washington - aho yabonaniye n'umushikiranganji wa Amerika ajejwe kwivuna abansi Lloyd Austin - Wallace yavuze ko Vladimir Putin ari we wenyene "ashobora kumenya iyo azoshikana igihugu"
 Ati: "Impera n'imperuka ategerezwa kwemera ko yataye umutwe
 "Uko vyogenda kwose, reka tuvuge ko Ubusuriya ari igihugu giciriritse gusumba uko cari kimeze imbere y'iki gitero"
 Wallace avuga kandi ko igisirikare c'Uburusiya "gishaje" kandi ko gishobora kugira ingorane zo gusubira kwiyubaka kubera ibihano ruhasha igihugu cafatiwe
 Vyongeye, Wallace avuga ko yemera ko Ubushinwa bugenda butinya ibiriko bikorwa n'Uburusiya, bukabona ko atari vyiza mu bijanye n'ubudandaji
 Ati: "Si incuti yo kwizera
 Ntushobora kumwizera ngo uherezeko"

Prezida w'Uburundi Evariste Ndayishimiye avuga ko imigwi yitwaje ibigwanisho isavye ibiganiro reta yiwe itokwanka
 Yabivugiye mu kiganiro c'amasaha atandatu yahaye abamenyeshamakuru bakorera mu Burundi ku murwa mukuru w'ubutunzi w'Uburundi, Bujumbura, ku wa kabiri
 Mu migwi yitwaje ibigwanisho ishingiye mu buseruko bwa Repuburika  ya Demokrasi ya Congo, harimwo iyamuka mu Burundi,  Red Tabaraba na FNL
 Reta y'Uburundi ariko ivuga ko umugwi nka Red Tabara ari umugwi w'iterabwoba, iwagiriza  bimwe mu bitero vy'amagrenade   mu gisagara ca Bujumbura mu mwaka uheze
 Ku kibazo c'uko bene iyo migwi isavye ibiganiro yokwemera, prezida Ndayishmiye yishuye ati  "N'uwutari Red Tabara, reta ijejwe kuguma yumviriza abana b'igihugu, igatora umuti w'ibibazo vyose bayishikirije
" BBC ntiraronka imihari nka Red Taraba kugira igire ico ishikirije ku vyaraye bivuzwe n'umukuru w'Uburundi
 Mu kwezi guheze abakuru b'ibihugu vy'akarere k'ibiyaga binini, bahuriye mu nama i Nairobi ku kibazo co kugarukana umutekano muri Congo harangwa imigwi myinshji yitwaje ibigwanisho
 Basavye umukuru w'igihugu ca Congo kugira ibiganiro n'imigwi y'abanye-Congo, iyamuka mu bindi bihugu nayo gutaha iwabo, yose ata kindi ibanje gusaba canke naho ice irwanywa n'ingabo z'akarere zigiye gushingwa ubwo nyene
 Umukuru w'igihugu c'Uburundi yari yitavye iyo nama asubiye mu Burundi yamahamagariye iyo "migwi y'abicanyi" gutaha
 Mw'itangazo, Red Tabara yavuze ko atari vyiza gukoresha  amajambo y'agasuzuguro ku "bavukagihugu nka we bahunze ku mvo zizwi", usaba prezida Ndayishimiye "gushiraho ibikenewe vya poritike kugira iryo tahuka ribe
" Uwo  mugwi uvuga ko umaze amezi atandatu uriko uragwana n'ingabo reta y'Uburundi yarungitse ku butaka bwa Congo kuwuhiga
 Reta z'Uburundi na Congo zompi zirahakana ko hari ingabo z'Uburundi ziri ku butaka bwa Congo
 Amashirahamwe adaharanira ivyicaro vya poritike aho muri Congo yo avuga ko hari ingabo z'Uburundi zajabutse ku butaka bwa Congo mu karere ka Uvira
 N'ubwa mbere umukuru w'Uburundi yemeye y'uko imigwi yamuka mu Burundi isavye ibiganiro reta itovyanka harimwo na Red Tabara  yise 'umugwi  w'iterabwoba ukorana na ADF"
 Atawe avuze izina, prezida Ndayishimiye yavuze ko ibiganiro ari vyo vyatumye bamwe mu banyaporitike batavuga rumwe na reta bari barahungiye hanze y'igihugu batahuka
 Muri abo harimwo Jeremie Ngendakumana yahoze ari umukuru w'umugambwe uri ku butegetsi, CNDD FDD, ariko aza kudacana uwaka nawo kuva mu 2015
 Prezida Ndayishimiye ati: "Na barya b'i Buraya,  barya banyaporitike mwibaza ko bataha gute? None ntitwama turiko turaganira
  Naho uba waracumuye burya ndababwire, igito gitabwa iwabo
 "
Mu kiganiro cihariye na BBC Gahuzamiryango, Miss Burundi 2022 avuga ko kuba hari abatashimye ko ari we yatahukanye intsinzi ata ntege vyamuciye ko ahubwo vyamwongereye ingoga
 Kelly Michelle Ngaruko yatahukanye intsinzi mw'ihiganwa ryabereye i Bujumbura ku wa gatandatu uheze
 Intsinzi yiwe ntiyavuzweko rumwe n'abakurikiranye iryo higanwa
 Atangazwa ko ariwe abaye uwa mbere mu bari mu birori hari abahagututse berekena ko batemera ko ariwe we yari akwiye ikibanza ca mbere
 Kelly Ngaruko yabwiye BBC ko ivyo aho kumuca intege ahubwo "vyampaye inguvu
" Agira ati: "Vyatumye ntangara ko abantu benshi bari bahanze amaso rino higanwa
 "Numva umenga vyanteye inguvu… barabishigikiye, kandi barifuza kubona umwigeme w'umurundikazi hari igikorwa atanze
" Miss Burundi 2022 avuga ko abatashimye ingene yatowe boshinga amaso ivyo agiye kuzorangura
 Ivyo navyo ngo bishingiye ku mugambi wiwe wo guteza imbere no gushigikira umwigeme w'umurundikazi abicishihe ku budandaji
 Kandi avuga ko yari asanzwe abikora kuva mu mwaka uheze
 Ati: "Ndabashira mu migwi, aho bigishwa, bagakurikiranwa kugira batanguze ubudandaji bwabo
" Umwigeme Ngaruko avuga ko asanzwe akorana n'isandugu itanga ingurane (microfinance)
 "Nzobandanya ndabikora uko nahora" mu kubaha ingurane kugira batanguze ubudandaji
 Ku mvo yatumye ashira imbere umwigeme avuga ko ari kubera yasanze ari we "dukunda gusiga inyuma, tugafasha abamama, abasore, mugabo kenshi umwigene barakunda kumwibagira
" Kelly Michelle avuga ko ihiganwa rya Miss rirengeye gushira imbere ubwiza bw'umubiri
 Ati: "Impanuro notanga ku mwigeme w'umurundikazi n'ukubandanya akora kugirango yerekane, abicishije mu bikorwa vyiwe, ko agaciro kiwe gasumba ubwiza abantu babona
"
Umushikirizamanza wo ku rwego rwo hejuru wa Paraguay yarwanije imirwi y'inkozi z'ikibi mu gihugu ciwe yishwe arashwe mu gihe yari mu karuhuko k'ubugeni muri Colombia
 Marcelo Pecci yari ku mweha (beach/plage) mw'izinga rya Baru rigenderwa cane n'ingenzi igihe yicwa n'abagabo babiri bari bitwaje inkoho
 Amasaha make imbere y'uko araswa, umugore we yari yatangaje kuri Instagram ko yibungenze
 Prezida wa Paraguay Mario Abdo Benitez yavuze ko iraswa rya Pecci ari "ubwicanyi bw'agahomerabunwa"
 Umugore wiwe, umunyamakuru Claudia Aguilera, avuga ko abagabo babiri babegereye bari ku mweha ukwa bonyene imbere y'uko umugabo wiwe araswa
 Avuga ko atari bwigere agira ubwoba gutyo
 Aguilera yabwiye ikinyamakuru El Tiempo ati: "Abagabo babiri bateye Marcelo
 Baje mu bwato buto, ariko sinabonye neza"
 Avuga ko umwe muri abo bicanyi yasohotse hanyuma "ata n'ijambo na rimwe avuze aca arasa Marcelo amasasu abiri, rumwe rwamugemye mu maso urundi mu mugongo"
 Ihoteri Decameron aba bageni bashikiyemwo yasohoye itangazo aho ivuga ko "abicanyi bashitse ku mweha


hanyuma bica umwe mu bashitsi bacu"
 Umushikirizamanza wundi w'umunya Paraguay, Augusto Salas, umugenzi wa Pecci, avuga ko iki gitero gisa n'igifitaniye "isano na magendo y'ibiyayuramutwe"
 Itororokanirizo ry'amakuru AFP ryandika ko Salas yagie ati: "Rero ivyo nivyo bizonguma mu mutwe gushika habaye ayandi makuru atandukanye"
 Umukuru w'igipolisi ca Colombia n'abajejwe amatohoza bo muri Paraguay bashitse ahabereye iri bara
 Abategetsi bo muri Amerika nabo nyene bazofasha amatohoza, nk'uko bivugwa n'umukuru w'igipolisi ca Colombia, Jenerali Jorge Luis Vargas
 Pecci yanonosoye ibijanye n'ubukozi bw'ikibi bukorwa n'imirwi y'inkozi z'ikibi, magendo y'ibiyayuramutwe, kunyereza amafaranga no guterera iterabwoba
 Mu 2020 yakoze amatohoza ku rubanza rw'uwahoze ari umukinyi w'umupira wa Brésil, Ronaldinho, yari yahagaritswe ariko agerageza kwinjira muri Paraguay akoresheje igitabo c'inzira ca Paraguay c'amanyanga
 Perezida Marcelo Abdo wa Paraguay  yanditse kuri Twitter ati: "Igandagurwa bunyamaswa ry'umushikirizamanza Marcelo Pecci muri Colombia ryashavuje igihugu cose ca Paraguay"
 "Turiyamirije twivuye inyuma iri bara kandi twiyemeje kwongereza inguvu mu kurwanya ubukozi bw'ikibi bukorwa n'imirwi y'inkozi z'ikibi ikorera hamwe"

Umuvugizi wa reta ya Zimbabwe avuga ko inzovu zimaze kwica abantu 60 gushika ubu uno mwaka gusa
