 Muri uno mwaka honyene, abanya-Zimbabwe 60 baramaze gutakaza ubuzima kubera inzovu, abandi 50 barakomereka
 Mu 2021, 72 nibo batswe ubuzima
 Zimbabwe izotegura ikoraniro ku kibazo c'inzovu uno mwaka"
 Mu karere kamwe, Bubi, inzovu "zaronye imirima zisiga yera ubu zikaba ziriko zitera zija mu mihana", nk'uko yavyanditse
 Avuga kandi ko ziriko zinjira mu mishamirano n'abantu bikaziviramwo gukomereka, ibi navyo bigatuma ziterwa "n'uburakari hamwe ata n'uwushobora no kuzitambika imbere"
 Bivugwa ko muri Zimbabwe haharurwa inzovu 100
000 kandi igitigiri kibandanya ciyongera
 Umuhinga umwe mu bijanye n'ubuzima bwo mu mashamba, Tinashe Farawo, yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru AFP ko ibintu bishobora kuba nabi
 AFP yasubiyemwo amajambo yiwe avuga ati: "Ibintu bishobora kuba nabi mu gihe turiko twegereza ici, aho amasho y'inyamaswa zizozunguruka irya n'ino zirondera amazi n'imfungurwa"

