Umunyamakuru w'umunyamerika akomoka muri Palestina yishwe arashwe mu gihe yariko atanga amakuru kuri Al Jazeera ku gitero c'ingabo za  Israel mu gisagara ca Jenin kiri mu karere ka Cisjordanie/West Bank kigaruriwe na Israel
 Iki kinyamakuru gifise icicaro muri Qatar kivuga ko Sherine Abu Aqla w'imyaka 51 yishwe "n'ibigirankana" n'ingabo za Israel
 Uwafata amasanamu bakorana nawe yakomeretse
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Israel avuga ko "bisa n'uko" barashwe n'abantu bitwaje ibirwanisho b'abanye-Palestina igihe haba ukurasana
 Ibi bibaye mu gihe imishamirano hagati ya Israel na Palestina igenda yiyongera
 Umukuru w'ubutegetsi bwa Palestina yagiriza reta ya Israel ko ari yo yakoze ico yita "icaha c'agahomerabunwa"
 Igisirikare ca Israel kivuga ko ingabo zaco n'abajejwe umutekano bakoze igitero kw'ikambi y'impunzi ya Jenin mu gaturuturu ko kuri uno wa gatatu mu ntumbero yo "guhagarika abikekwa ko ari intagondwa"
 "Muri ico gikorwa, abanye-Palestina bitwaje inkoho baharurwa muri mirongo barashe bongera batera ibiturika ku basirikare bacu
 Aba basirikare bivunye abo bitwaje inkoho"
 Umushikiranganji wa Palestina ajejwe amagara y'abantu yavuze ko Sherine Abu Aqla yarashwe urusasu mu mutwe igihe yariko yegeranya amakuru kuri ico gitero
 Yaciye anyarukanwa ku bitaro ameze nabi cane, mu nyuma atangazwa ko yacikanye
 Uwundi munyamakuru w'umunye-Palestina akorera Al Jazeera nyene afata amasanamu, Ali Samoudi, yarashwe mu mugongo ariko akaba ameze neza aho ariko aravurirwa mu bitaro, nk'uko bivugwa n'uyu mushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu
 Al Jazeera isubiramwo Samoudi avuga ati: "Twari tugiye gufata amashusho y'igikorwa ca gisirikare ca Israel ubwo nyene baca baraturasa batanadusavye ko tuhava canke ngo tureke gufata amashusho
 "Urusoro rwa mbere rwafashe jewe, urwa kabiri rufata Sherine
 Yongerako ati: "Nta munye-Palestina n'umwe yariko arivuna igihe ivyo vyaba"
 Itangazo rya Al Jazeera rivuga riti: "Mu bwicanyi bw'agahomerabunwa, buhonyanga amategeko mpuzamakungu, ingabo za Israel zigaruriye ubutaka bwacu zagandaguye umunyamakuru wa Al Jazeera muri Palestine Sherine Abu Aqla zimurashe amasasu mu gatondo ka kare


mu gihe yari ku kazi kiwe nk'umumenyeshamakuru, bigaragara neza ko yari yambaye umwambaro w'akazi umwerekana ko ari umunyamakuru"
 Iki kinyamakuru gitera akamo amakungu ko yiyamiriza reta n'igisirikare vya Israel kuri "iri raswa n'igandagurwa" ry'umunyamakuru
 Umukuru w'ubutegetsi bwa Palestina Mahmoud Abbas ariyamiriza iraswa rya  Abu Aqla na Samoudi, akavuga ko "kurasa abanyamakuru biri muri poritike yo kwifatira uturere mu ntumbero yo gukora amabi ata camira"
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Israel Naftali Bennett yagirije Perezida Abbas gushikiriza "ibirego bidafise ishingiro"
 Mw'itangazo yasohoye, yavuze ati: "Ku makuru tumaze kwegeranya, bisa n'uko abanye-Palestina bitwaje ibirwanisho - ico gihe barasa mu rudavagi - aribo bafise uruhara mw'igandagurwa ry'uyu munyamakuru"
 "Mbere abanye-Palestina i Jenin bafashwe amashusho bariko barirata: 'Twarashe umusirikare, aryamye hasi'
  Hagati aho, nta musirikare n'umwe [wa Israel] yakomeretse, ibi bikerekana ko intagondwa z'abanye-Palestina ari bo bashobora kuba barashe uyu munyamakuru"
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere Bennett avuga ko Israel yasavye ubutegetsi bwa Palestina ko bokorera hamwe amatohoza kugira ukuri kumenyekane, ariko ko abategetsi ba Palestina gushika ubu bavyanse
 Igisirikare ca Israel kirakunze gukora ibitero mw'ikambi y'impunzi ya Jenin
 Barongereje ibi bitero muri ino misi ya vuba inyuma y'urukurikirane rw'ibitero bikorwa n'abarabu b'abanya-Israel n'abanye-Palestina ku mabarabara ya Israel no muri Cisjordanie mu ndwi ziheze vyahitanye ubuzima bw'abanya- Israel 17 n'abanya-Ukraine babiri
 Abanye-Palestina n'imiburiburi 26 barishwe - harimwo abarwanyi barashwe igihe bakora ivyo bitero, canke abitwaje ibirwanisho n'abasivire bishwe mu bitero vya Israel n'ukurasana muri Cisjordanie
 Ibikorwa vya gisirikare vya Israel vyashimikiye ku karere ka Jenin, ahavugwa ko ariho hazananye bane mu banya-Palestina bakoze ivyo bitero muri Israel

Misire zakoreshejwe mu gisagara ca Odesa zishobora kuba ari izo ku ntwaro y'aba Soviyeti - ariko ivyo zononye ntibiharurwa
 Abategetsi b'ico gisagara bemeza ko umusi w'ejo igenekerezo rya 9 Rusama (5) Odesa yatewe misire icenda hakoreshejwe indege
 Videwo yacishijwe ku mbuga hwaniro n'igisirikare ca Ukraine yerekana abasirikare bariko baca mu bihomoka vy'inyubakwa yahoze ari iy'ubucuruzi (centre commercial/shopping centre) n'iy'ububiko
 Umwotsi mwinshi wakwiragiye hagati muri ico gisagara gifise kahise karekare
 Ariko kubera amategeko yo kutava muhira amabarabara yagaragara igihe izo misire zaterwa isaha zine n'iminota 30 z'ijoro ryakeye
 Abategetsi bavuga ko umuntu umwe yahasize ubuzima abandi batanu nabo barakomereka bakaba bajanywe mu bitaro
 Ibi bitero vyabaye mu masaha y'ijoro ry'ejo ku wa mbere, umusi umukuru w'Inama y'ishirahamwe ry'abanyabulaya yari yagendeye ico gisagara
 Charles Michel yavuze ko yabonye ibigega vyuzuye intete, ingano n'ibigori i Odesa birindiriye gushorwa hanze - ariko bikaba vyarazibiwe
 Ubwoba bw'uko hashobora kuba ikibazo c'imfungurwa kw'isi ni ikintu cagarutsweko na Perezida Zelensky mw'ijambo ryiwe yashikirije ejo mw'ijoro
 Yavuze ko ibihugu bitari bike bigeze ahatemba kubera ubukene bwimfungurwa kandi ko ibintu bishobora "kuba, mvugishije ukuri, nabi cane", mu gihe vyokwanka ko Ukraine ishora ivyimburwa hanze
 Ibi biri uko mu gihe ibitero vy'urutavanako bibandanya mu buseruko bwa Ukraine
 Haravugwa intambara zikomeye mu micungararo y'ibisagara vya Rubizhne na Bilohorivka - vyompi biri mu ntara ya Donbas
 Hagati aho, umutegetsi wo ku rwego rwo hejuru mu bushikiranganji bwo kwivuna abansi bwa Amerika avuga ko mu misi mike iheze, Uburusiya ata kintu kinini bwashitseko, n'aho bwigaruriye igisagara ca Popasna kiri mu buseruko
 Uyo mutegetsi abandanya avuga kandi ko igisagara ca Kharkiv kikiri mu minwe ya reta ya Ukraine
 Mw'ijambo ryiwe, Perezida Zelensky yagabishije ko Uburusiya buriko "buhonyora  mu mahwa amwe" n'ayo abigeze gutera Ukraine bahonyoyemwo, yongerako ati "nta mwansi n'umwe yigeze ashinga imizi hano"
 I Mariupol naho, umushikiranganji wo kwivuna abansi wa Ukraine avuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya ziriko "ziracucagira ibibombe" ku ruganda rw'ivyuma rwa Azovstal, aho amajana n'amajana y'abarwanyi ba Ukraine babandanya bahanganye n'ibitero vy'Uburusiya
 Petro Andriushchenko, umuhanuzi w'umukuru w'igisagara ca Mariupol avuga ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zatanguye kugota urwo ruganda inyuma y'aho amamodoka ya ONU aviriye mu karere ka Donetsk
 Avuga ko Abarusiya bariko bagerageza kubomora ikiraro gikoreshwa mu guhungisha abantu, mu ntumbero yo kuzibirirayo abarwanyi babandanya barwanira urwo ruganda
 Umugore w'umusirikare wa Ukraine arwanira muri urwo ruganda avuga ko yamubwiye ko ibintu bibandanya biba nabi, mu gihe amazi agenda abaherana, amajana n'amajana y'abasirikare bakomeretse nabo bakaba bakizibiriweyo
 Avugana na BBC, Yuliia Feosiuk yavuze ko igihe avugana ubwa nyuma n'umugabo wiwe yamusavye ko yobaronderera ibintu "bishobora kubongerera imisi yo kubaho ata mazi igihe kirekire gishoboka"
 Yuliia Feosiuk avuga ko umugabo wiwe yamubariye ko abasirikare bababa 700 bakomeretse bakizibiwe muri urwo ruganda, kandi ko ibiziga vy'abasirikare bapfuye bikibitswe muri vya vyuma bikanyisha

Inyuma y'ukwiyongera kw'ibitigiri vy'abanyuruzwa muri ino myaka ya vuba,  Afrika y'Epfo iri mu bihugu bifise ibitigiri binini cane vy'abantu banyuruzwa kw'isi, nk'uko bivugwa na Mpho Lakaje ari i  Johannesburg
 Mu ntango, Lesego Tau ntiyasimbwe n'umutima igihe umuntu atazwi yugurura umuryango w'inyuma w'imodoka yiwe ya Mercedes C-Class agaca yiteramwo
 Yari yayihagaritse hanze y'isoko rya kijambere (centre commercial/shopping mall) i  Johannesburg akaba yariko yandikira mugenziwe kuri terefone imbere y'uko aja kugura utuntu dukeya two guteramirako ku mugoroba w'uyo musi
 Avuga ibi bintu vyamubayeko mu kwa gatandatu guheze, yabwiye BBC ati: "Namurabiye mu kiyo nkaguma nibaza nti: 'Uyu muntu ivyo ari vyo vyose araterwa n'isoni ni yabona ko yuriye imodoka atari yo',"
 Ariko rero uku ntikwari ukwihenda
 "Twararabanye mu maso nca ndamenya icari kigiye kuba"
 Iri ryari inyuruzwa
 Amezi atandatu imbere y'aha, umugwizatunga Yasin Bhiku yafatiwe mu kayira kaja muhira iwe, hafi ya Johannesburg, avuye mu musigiti
 Video ya CCTV yazungurutse cane ku mbuga hwaniro yerekana Bhiku yambaye agapira gasa n'ubururu n'ipantaro yirabura aganira neza n'umugenzi
 Haboneka abagabo babiri basohoka bavuye mu yindi modoka yari yahagaritswe ku rundi ruhande
 Ubwa mbere bateye bamwegera, hanyuma bamusimbirako aho Bhiku amariye kubona ivyo ari vyo akagerageza guhunga
 Yaraneshejwe aca yinjizwa mu modoka afatiweko inkoho
 Mu nyuma uyu mugwizatunga bagiye kumutora ataco yabaye arabohozwa n'igipolisi
 Uyu mugore Tau asanzwe afise ikompanyi ikora isuku i Pretoria na we nyene yaragerageje guhunga amaze kubona ko yagomba anyuruzwe
 Avuga ko yagerageje kwugurura umuryango w'imodoka yiwe, ariko uwundi mugabo yambaye nk'umukozi wo muri parikingi aca arazibira umuryango
 Uyu mugabo yari yicaye inyuma yaciye yerekana ko afise inkoho aca ategeka uyu mugore Tau kuvana iyi modoka muri ico kigo c'akaguriro
 Ari mu nzira, yarategetswe guhagarika imodoka, maze uwundi muntu aca yinjiramwo
 Bamaze kugenda ibirometero hafi 15 baja hagati mu gihugu muri urwo rugendo ruteye ubwoba, aba bari bamunyuruje bategetse Tau guhagarara
 Haciye haza imodoka itukura, umuntu umwe aca arururuka, amwaka amakarata y'ibanki hanyuma amutegeka kumubwira ibiharuro-kabanga
 "Abandi bantu bari mu modoka


baciye batangura kwinjira mu makarata yanje atandukanye
 Bariko barakurako amahera"
 Muri uwo mwanya nyene, abo bantu bari bamunyuruje babandanije bamukubita mu mutwe n'inkoho, bamutegeka kwongereza urugero rw'amafaranga ashobora gukurako
 Aya magorwa yarabandanije mu kiringo c'amasaha ane
 Igihe kimwe, yumvise umuntu kuri terefone bariko bavugana avuga ngo: "Mukureho
 Ahacu twahejeje"
 Tau ati: "Naciye niha amahoro kuko nabona ko bari bagiye kunyica, ariko nariyumviriye, nca mbona ko nategerezwa kwirwanira
 Ni ngombwa turwane
 Nimba bagiye kunyica, nshobora no kurwana"
 Yararwanye arashobora kuva mu modoka ariko abari bamunyuruje baramucakiye baca batangura kumukubita
 Yahavuye abacoroka ariruka mw'ibarabara yinyuranganya mu mamodoka
 Ibi vyamushikiye n'ivyashikiye Bhiku si vyo vyonyene
 Mu kwa kabiri, umushikiranganji ajejwe igipolisi Bheki Cele yamenyesheje ko mu mezi atatu ya nyuma ya 2021 habaye 2
605 bituye ubutegetsi bavuga ivy'inyuruzwa
 Mu myaka cumi kuva 2010, inyuruzwa ryariyongereye incuro zirenga zibiri muri Afrika y'Epfo, kandi  abantu 10 kuri 100
000 baranyuruzwa, nk'uko bivugwa n'ikigo ca Afrika y'Epfo cigisha ibijanye n'umutekano, Institute for Security Studies
  Ni kimwe mu biharuro binini cane vy'abanyuruzwa kw'isi
 Mu 2018, umushikiranganji Cele yemereye abanyagihugu ko yari agiye gushira imbere ukurwanya inyuruza
 Abahuye n'ivyo vyago barabagumya  ku nguvu, bamwe bakaronderwako ingwati, abandi amakonte yabo y'amabanki akavanwako amafaranga yose, canke naho bagakorerwa ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina
 Hari bamwe baruhira kuhatakariza ubuzima, n'aho urugero rutazwi neza
 Mu ntumbero yo kugerageza kurwanya amabi nk'aya, igipolisi carashinze umurwi ujejwe kurwanya inyuruzwa
 Ikintu kimwe kimaze kuboneka ni uko abanyuruza abantu basa n'abakorera mu mirwi kandi bigakorwa hakurikijwe integuro kanaka aho usanga buri muntu afise ico ajejwe, nk'uko umuvugizi w'igipolisi Athlenda Mathe yabibwiye BBC
 "Inderetsi ni barya bakurikirana uwugiye kunyuruzwa
 Abamufata ni barya baca bamutwara"
 Abanyuruza abantu akenshi banyonga amamodoka anyaruka cane kandi ugasanga bafise ibirwanisho
 "Hakaba rero n'abandi bamugumya 


gushika harishwe ingwati"
 Ariko muri ako kabi, hariho umuhinga akora ubushakashatsi akanamukurikiranira hagufi
 Koroneri Marthe avuga ati: "Uwuri hejuru ya bose ashobora kuba ari umuntu abayeho neza kandi adashobora gukora ako kabi kabishe"
 Iyi mirwi y'inkozi z'ikibi ifise amashami mu bihugu vyo hanze nk'igihugu kibanyi ca Mozambike  gushika mbere no mu bihugu vya kure nko muri Pakistani
 Basa n'abizizira abagwizatunga bifise, bafise ubushobozi bwo kuriha ingwati, ariko bamwe mu babikorerwa bava mu turere tw'abantu babayabaye mbere n'abana ntibasigwa inyuma
 Gérard Labuschagne asanzwe agiriranira ibiganiro vyo kubohoza abanyurujwe ku giti ciwe avuga ko inyuruza ryo ku rwego rwo hejuru ryiyongereye
 Ingwati ishobora gushika ku miriyoni zitatu z'amadorari y'abanyamerika
 Labuschagne agira ati: "Imirwi y'inkozi z'ikibi muri Mozambike no mu tundi turere twa Afrika ubu yarafashe ingingo ko, uko vyogenda kwose, Afrika y'Epfo ari igihugu ciza co gukoreramwo ubukozi bw'ikibi nk'ubu, kandi iramaze kubukora neza"
 Ku mbuga hwaniro, bamwe babona ko ukutubahiriza amategeko kwatumye Afrika y'Epfo iba ikirimbiro ry'imirwi y'inkozi z'ikibi iva mu mpande zose z'isi
 Imbere y'abanyagihugu barakaye, igipolisi kiremera ko hakiri igikorwa kinini ariko Koroneri Mathe avuga ko bamaze gutera intambwe
 "Kuva iyi mirwi imenyekanye, tumaze guhagarika abikekwa muri ubwo bukozi bw'ikibi 115, harimwo abanya-Pakistani, abanya-Mozambike hamwe kandi n'abanya-Afrika y'Epfo"
 Umwe muri abo bafashwe ni Faizel Charloos w'imyaka 43 yafashwe agapfungwa mu kwa gatatu
 Azwi ko ari we yateguye urukurikirane rw'inyuruzwa riherutse
 Mu gitero cakozwe n'igipolisi ku matungo atari make afitaniye isano nawe i Johannesburg, ibiyayuramutwe, amafaranga n'amamodoka meza meza ni vyo vyatowe
 Charloos aherutse kurengutswa mu bucamanza, ari kumwe n'abandi batari bake, ku birego vyo kunyuruza abantu
 Ntaco arabivugako
 Vyabonetse ko afise ubwenegihugu bubiri ubwa Afrika y'Epfo na Mozambike
 'Igipolisi ntigitabara abanyuruzwa' Mu bindi vyabaye muri Ndamukiza (4), igipolisi carashoboye kurokora umwana w'umukobwa w'imyaka ine yari yibwe kw'ishure rimwe i Johannesburg n'umugore yigize umurezi wiwe
 Imbere yaho, uwari yamunyuruje yari yasavye ibihumbi n'ibihumbi vy'amadorari kugira ngo amusubize
 Ariko abantu bane baje guhagarikwa hafi y'inyubakwa y'idandarizo baje gutora ingwati
 N'aho bashitse kuri ivyo, Labuschagne ntiyemera ko igipolisi kiriko kiratsinda uru rugamba
 "Turamaze kubona incuro imwe canke zibiri bahagarikwa
 Ariko bwinshi muri ubu bukozi bw'ikibi, abapolisi ntibabohoza ababa banyurujwe aho bapfungiwe
 Baza kurekurwa hatanzwe aya mafaranga"
 Uyu mugore Tau yagize amahirwe arashobora kubaca mu ryahumye, ariko abari bamunyuruje bamunyaze amadorari 1400 y'abanyamerika
 Amarorerwa yamubayeko yaramuhahamuye mbere n'umuryango wiwe ukaba waratuntuye
 "Papa wanje si umuntu arira, ariko yarakoroye amosozi
 Yaguma yumva y'uko yategerezwa kuba yankingiye"
 "Haracari uruhande rumwe rwanje rwapfuye uwo musi"

Manchester City yashitse ku masezerano yo kugura umusatirizi w'igihangange ava muri Norvege, Erling Haaland, imukuye muri Borussia Dortmund
 Haaland w'imyaka 22, azotangura gukinira City muri Mukakaro (7), mu gihe iyo kipe yamaze kwemera kurekura imiriyoni 60 z'ama euro yasabwa mu masezerano yiwe
 Aya masezerano aheraheje umwete w'iyi kipe wo kurondera umusatirizi asubirira uwayinjirije vyinshi bimaze kuboneka, Sergio Aguero, yagiye muri Barcelona ici riheruka
 City yagize iti "Turashobora kwemanga yuko twashitse ku mwumvikano wo kugura umusatirizi Erling Haaland"
 "Kuza kw'uyu mukinyi kurindiriye kwuzuzwa kw'ibisabwa vyose mu vyumvikanywe nawe
" Haaland yarinjije ibitsindo 85 mu nkino 88 amaze gukinira Dortmund kuva yaza muri iyo kipe avuye muri Red Bull Salzburg muri Nzero (1) 2020
 Ibihangange vyo muri La Liga, Real Madrid na Barcelona, navyo vyari vyavuganye na Haaland bishaka kumugura, ariko aca ahitamwo kuja Etihad Stadium
 Aho yavuga kare kuri uno wa kabiri, umumenyereza wa Manchester City, Pep Guardiola, yavuze ko adashobora kuvuga ku bakinyi bari mu gusinya kubera imvo z'amategeko
 Yongeyeko ati "Abantu bose barazi uko bimeze
 Sinshobora kuvuga kuko sinkunda kuvuga kuri kazoza canke ku mwaka w'inkino ukurikira"
 Abajijwe akamaro umusatirizi mushasha yogirira iyi kipe isanzwe ari yo ifise igikompe ca Premier League, Guardiola yagize ati: "Abakinyi bashasha bama bafasha mu gukomeza ikipe
 Ariko nta musatirizi umwe canke myugariro yokemura ibibazo vyo kuzibira canke kwinjiza
 "Ikipe itegerezwa kwama ifise intumbero ya kazoza
 Ivyemezo ikipe ifata ndabizi kandi ndabishigikiye 100%
" Kugurwa kw'uyu mukinyi nikwo kuzoba gukomeye kurusha ukundi kwose muri rino ci

Uburusiya buvuga ko abibaza ko bushobora gutangaza intambara yeruye na Ukraine kuri uno musi w'intsinzi ari ivyiyumviro bidafise ishingiro
 Uyu musi iki gihugu gihimbaza intsinzi yaco ku ba Nazi b'Abadagi mu 1945, abenshi bakagenda berekana amasanamu y'incuti zabo zarwanye iyo ntambara
 Gushika ubu, Moscou iracahakana ko iri mu ntambara, ahubwo ikavuga ko iki gitero muri Ukrane ari "igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare"
 Ariko abategetsi bo mu bihugu vy'Uburengero babona ko Perezida Vladimir Putin ashobora gukoresha idefire y'uno musi agatangaza intambara yeruye
 Gusa gushika ubu aracarigumije, abantu bakaba biteze ko ashobora kurishira ahabona mw'ijambo aza gushikiriza mw'idefire ibera mu Kibanza Gitukura (Place rouge/Red Square), bakabandanya bafise amakenga
 Aha ntibibagira ingene imbere y'uko atanguza intambara ku wa 24 Ruhuhuma (2), abategetsi b'Uburusiya baguma batera agashinyaguro ibihugu vy'Uburengero vyaguma bimenyesha ko ico gihugu kiri mu gutanguza intambara
 Ico gihe bavuga ko bwari "ubwoba burangwa mu bihugu vya Bulaya hamwe na propaganda"
  Uburusiya ariko bwahise butera ico gihugu, mbere abanya Ukraine benshi bakaba baguye mu gahundwe
 Rero mu bintu bike vyitezwe ko ashikiriza ni amajambo amwe amwe y'intsinzi amaze gushikako mu ntego yari afise hamwe no kuvuga ko abansi baneshejwe
 Ibihugu vyo mu Burengero kandi vyitezwe kugabishwa ku mfashanyo yavyo biha Ukraine, Putin akavyagiriza ko ari vyo bituma ata kiboneka ashikako mu ntambara y'Uburusiya mu ntara ya Donbas
 Ni wo musi wa mbere ukomeye uhimbazwa mu gihugu aho bibuka intsinzi y'icahoze ari Reta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abasoviyeti ku ba Nazi b'Abadagi
 Ibirori vyitezwe gutangura umwanya n'umwanya, Perezida Putin akaba yitezwe kugerageza guhamagarira abanyagihugu gufata mu mugongo iyi ntambara ya Ukraine
 Ku ntwaro ya Vladimir Putin, Umusi w'Intsinzi wagiye uba uwo kwerekanirako inguvu n'ibikoresho rutura vya gisirikare, hamwe no kwibuka abatanze ubuzima bwabo mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose
 Abasoviyeti bababa imiriyoni 27 baraguye muri iyo ntambara, gushika ubu iki kikaba ari co gitigiri kinini c'abahitanywe n'intambara kw'isi yose mu gihugu ico ari co cose
 Mu birori vy'uno musi, Uburusiya bwitezwe kwerekana ibihumbi n'ibihumbi vy'ingabo, ibifaru, vya muzinga na za misire zirasa kure biza kuzunguruka mu gisagara ca Moscow mu kwerekana inguvu za Kremlin
 Ariko ibirori vy'uno musi bifise iyindi nsiguro mu gihe Uburusiya bumaze amezi atatu mu ntambara n'igihugu kibanyi ca Ukraine ikigoranye, kandi gushika ubu bukaba ata ntsinzi ya gisirikare igaragara bwovuga ko bushobora kwishimira
 Vyabaye ngombwa ko ingabo z'Uburusiya zihindura umukenyuro mu gushira inguvu zose mu ntambara yo mu buseruko bwa Ukraine inyuma y'aho zinaniriwe no gufata umugwa mukuru Kyiv n'ibindi bisagara bikomakomeye
 Buca ari Umusi w'intsinzi, mu gihe igihugu ciwe kibandanya gitabagurika Prezida Volodymyr Zelensky wa Ukraine avuga ko Uburusiya "bwibagiye ibintu vyose vyatumye bushika ku ntsinzi zose bwagiye buronka mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose"
 Yavuze ko isi irangwa n'ubwigenge ishobora kubona ko Ukraine ari "umuhari w'ineza muri ino ntambara", yongerako y'uko Uburusiya buzotegerezwa "gutsindwa kubera ikibi cama gitsindwa"
 Ibihugu vy'Uburengero kandi vyafashe aka karyo k'Umusi w'Intsinzi kugira vyiyamirize ibikorwa vy'Uburusiya muri Ukraine
 Umushikiranganji wa mbere wa Canada, Justin Trudeau - nawe nyene akaba amaze kugendera Ukraine - yabwiye itororokanirizo ry'amakuru Reuters ko Perezida Vladimir Putin w'Uburusiya ariko "aja kubiri n'intumbero abantu benshi barwaniye bakanayipfira"
 Abategetsi b'umurwi G7 uhuriyemwo ibihugu bitunze kurusha ibindi kw'isi bavuga ko ibikorwa vya Putin "vyateje urubwa Uburusiya n'abanyagihugu  babwo babwitagniye"

Perezida Vladimir Putin avuga ko ibihugu vyo mu Burengero vyanse kwumviriza Uburusiya kubera vyari bifise izindi nteguro
 Mw'ijambo yavugiye ku kibanza 'gitukura' (PLace Roge/Red Square)  i Moscou, Putin yavuze ko ibihugu vy'Uburengero vyariko "bitegura gutera ubutaka bwacu, harimwo na Crimée /Crimea"
 Yabwiye ingabo ko intambara zirimwo ubu ziriko zirwanira umutekano w'Uburusiya
 Yabandanije ijambo ryiwe avuga ko "igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare" muri Ukraine   cari nkenerwa kandi ko caje "hageze"
 Avuga ko yabaye "ingingo nyayo" nk'igihugu cikukiye, gikomeye kandi cigenga
 Putin yavuze kandi ko igihugu kizokora "ibishoboka vyose" kigafata mu mugongo imiryango yose yaburiye mu ntambara ya Ukraine
 Ati: "Umusirikare uwo ari we wese apfuye adutera umubabaro"
 OTAN/NATO 'akaga gakomeye' ku Burusiya - Putin Perezida Vladimir Putin avuga ko imyaka itatu iheze yaranzwe n'icuka kibi n'ibindi bihugu vya Bulaya, hamwe na OTAN
 Avuga ko Uburusiya "bwasavye ibiganiro n'Ubulaya, ariko ntibashatse kutwumviriza", akavuga kandi ko buriko butegura ibindi bihano kuri Donbas mu burengero bwa Ukraine, aho avuga ko ubu ibikorwa vy'Uburusiya ari ho vyibanze
 "I Kyiv bahora bavuga ko bashobora kuronka ibirwanisho vya nikleyeri mu gihe OTAN yari yatanguye kwiga akarere katwegereye, ibi bikaba vyabonetse ko kari akaga ku gihugu cacu no ku mbibe zacu
 Ibintu vyose vyatwereka ko twategerezwa kurwana"
 Hagati aho, ibihugu vyinshi kw'isi n'amashirahamwe mpuzamakungu nka ONU, bifata ko igitero c'Uburusiya muri Ukraine ari igitero giteye kubiri n'amategeko
 Putin yaciye asaba umunota wo kwunamira Abarusiya bapfiriye mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose ariko kandi n'abasirikare bariko bararwanira Uburusiya muri Donbas
 Nk'uko abatari bake bari bavyiteze, nta kintu gikomeye yatangaje mu migambi yoba afise
 Katarzyna Zysk, umurusiyakazi w'umuhinga mu vya gisirikare, yabwiye imboneshakure BBC News ko ata gitangaza kirimwo kwumva Vladimir Putin afatanya iyi ntambara ya Ukraine n'intambara ya kabiri y'isi yose, "mu gushimagiza kahise k'ubutegetsi bw'aba Soviyeti, mbere akerekana inkumbu afitiye Abasoviyeti, ikintu gikwiye mu Burusiya hose, ubu bikaba vyunyuwe n'abategetsi b'Uburusiya"
 Avuga ko yabandanije asubiramwo ivyo yagiriza OTAN ko yariko itegura igitero ca nikleyeri, yongera avuga ko Uburusiya burwanya "Aba-Nazi ba Ukraine"
 Zysk avuga ko ibi biri mu ntumbero yo kwerekana ko Uburusiya ari ikirindiro gisugerejwe kandi ko aho hose Uburusiya bwagiye bunanirwa kuva mu myaka ya 1990 yabaye amakosa y'ibihugu vy'uburengero
 Ati: "Yerekana ko Uburusiya buhohoterwa
 Ibi kandi ni mu ntumbero yo gusigura iyi ntambara"
 Avuga ko yatangajwe n'ukungene Putin atigeze avugamwo abahemu b'Abarusiya bakorana n'Uburengero kugira ngo ate mu mporero abo bose batumva iyi ntambara
 Avuga kandi ko bitangaje kwumva avuga ko Uburusiya buri mu ntambara na OTAN hamwe na Ukraine
 Ku ruhande rwiwe, Perezida Volodymyr Zelensky yasohoye video irimwo ubutumwa yahaye abanyagihugu mu guhimbaza intsinzi ku ba-Nazi b'Abadagi mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose, aho avuga ko igihugu ciwe kizotsinda intambara kirimwo n'Uburusiya
 Zelensky avuga kandi ko Ukraine idashobora kurekura "agace na gato k'ubutaka bwacu" ngo kigarurirwe n'Uburusiya
 Ati: "Turiko turarwanira intsinzi nshasha
 Ni inzira itoroshe ariko nta nkeka dufise ko dutegerezwa gutsinda"

Umukinyi nserukiraghihugu wa Repuburika ya Demokrasi ya Congo (RDC) Jody Lukoki, yatanguye gukina mu rwego rw'abakuze  mu mugwi wa Ajax wo mu Buhorandi, yapfuye ku myaka 29
 Lukoki yarakiniye kandi imigwi ya PEC Zwole,  Ludogorets yo muri Bulgarie hamwe na  Yeni Malatyaspor yo muri Turkia, ubu akaba yaheruka kwinjira muri  FC Twente yo mu Buhorandi
 FC Twente, mw'itangazo ku rubuga rwayo rwa internet, yavuze ko ''FC Twente yashegehswe kandi yababajwe cane n'ivyashitse
'' ''FC Twente isangiye umubabaro n'abiwe kandi ubifurije kwifata cane muri ibi bihe babuze umuntu akomeye cane''
 Icatumye urupfu rwa Lukoki  ntikiramenyekana
 Uwo mukinyi wo ku ruhande yari yinjiye muri FC Twente ku masezerano y'imyaka ibiri mu kwezi kwa gatandatu guheze ariko aca agira imvune ikomeye mw'ivi  mu kiringo co kwitegurira umwaka mushasha w'inkino
 Amasezerano yiwe na FC Twente yahagaritswe mu kwezi kwa  Ruhuhuma (ukwa 2), kubera ivyo umugwi wise ''ibintu bijanye n'ubuzima bwiwe''
 Zwolle nawo wavuze ''umubabaro n'intuntu'' inyuma y'urupfu rwa Lukoki, yinjirije igitsindo ca mbere uwo mugwi mw'ihiganwa rya Buraya kuva wakabaho
 Ku ndwi iheze uwo  mukinyi yari yashize kuri Instagram yiwe ubutumwa bw'uko  yari mu cumba co kwinonora (gym) yitegurira kugaruka inyuma y'imvune
 Lukoki yinjije ibitsindo bitanu mu nkino 35 na Ajax imbere y'uko yimukira muri Zwolle mu 2014
 Mu mwaka ukurikira yaciye aja muri  Ludogorets aho  yamaze imyaka itanu hanyuma agakina inkino 158 yinjijemwo ibitsindo 30
 Inyuma y'umwaka w'inkino wa 2020-2021 muri Turkia, yaciye asubira mu Buhorandi muri Twente
 Lukoki yaraserukiye Ubuhorandi ku rugero rw'abakiri bato ariko yatanguye kuba umukinyi nserukiragihugu wa RD Congo mu 2015
 Ubwa mu nyuma  mu nkino zitatu yakiniye Leopards ariko zose ari za kivamdimwe, hari mu rukino rwazihuje na Burkina Faso mu 2020

Umuvugabutumwa muri Nigeria ari mu yabira inyuma yo kubwira abantu ko azi irembo ribashikana mw'ijuru riri mu bumanuko bushira uburengero bw'ico gihugu, ariko ko kugira aribereke bategerezwa gutanga amafaranga
 Pasitori Ade Abraham yarezwe mu gipolisi n'umwe mu banywanyi biwe avuga ko uyo mu pasitori yamutangishije 310
000 y'amanaira (amafaranga yo muri Nigeria), angana n'amadorari y'abanyamerika 750, kugira ngo bashobore kubona iryo rembo avuga ko riri mu gisagara ca Araromi-Ugbeshi, mu ntara ya Ekiti
 Uyu muvugabutumwa yemereye BBC ko koko yabwiye abantu ivy'iryo rembo, akavuga ko ari "Imana akorera" yarimweretse mu ntumbero yo kuraba aho abanyashengero biwe bageza mu kwemera kwabo, ariko akavuga ko ata muntu n'umwe aramuha amafaranga
 Ishirahamwe ry'Abakristu muri Nigeria ryasohoye itangazo ryikurako uyo mupasitori Ade Abraham, igipolisi co mu ntara ya Ekiti naco kikaba cegeranije inzandiko z'abanywanyi b'ishengero ryiwe, kikaba catanguye amatohoza
 Ishengero rya Pasitori Ade Abraham ryahora rifise icicaro mu ntara ya Kogi, mu nyuma ryimukira mu ntara ya Kaduna, imbere y'uko ryimukira amaja mu bumanuko n'abanywanyi baryo, mw'ikambi yubatse mu ntara ya Ekiti
 Uyu munyashengero yamureze ku gipolisi yaciye yisubirira muhira iwe i Kaduna kuva ico gihe, ariko umugore wiwe yaranse kumukurikira, akavuga ko "igihe c'umunezero" cari kigiye gushika vuba
 Ariko uyu mugabo n'umugore badashaka ko amazina yabo amenyekana babwiye BBC ko babandanya bavugana kuri terefone umusi ku musi
 Pasitori Ade, azwi kandi kw'izina rya Noah Abraham (Nowa Aburahamu), aherutse kwerekanwa mw'ireresi yazungurutse cane, aho yariko asaba abasenga Imana gutera akamo incuti zabo ziri mu mahanga gutanga intererano y'amafaranga mu rusengero rwiwe

Vyabaye ibirori ngarukamwaka - idefire y'igisirikare ku Kibanza Gitukura (Place Rouge/Red Square) ku mugwa mukuru Moscou/Moscow no mu bindi bisagara mu Burusiya ku wa 9 Rusama (5), mu guhimbaza intsinzi ku ba Nazi b'Abadagi mu 1945
 Ku butegetsi bwa Vladimir Putin, Umusi w'Intsinzi (Victory Day) wagizwe umusi wo gushira ahabona inguvu za gisirikare, mu kwerekana abasirikare  n'ibirwanisho vyabwo,  ariko kandi kakaba akaryo ko kwibuka abahitanywe n'Intambara ya Kabiri y'Isi yose
 Imiriyoni 27 z'Abasoviyeti nibo bahatikiriye, igitigiri kinini gushika ubu gusumba ibindi bihugu vyose
 Ibirori vy'uno mwaka, bifise iyindi nsiguro
 Uburusiya bumaze amezi atari make mu ntambara n'igihugu kibanyi ca Ukraine kandi gushika ubu nta ntsinzi ya gisirikare ikomeye bwovuga ko bushobora kwishimira
 Abasirikare bagize uruhara muri ino ntambara bazodefira imbere y'intwazangabo nkuru n'umukuru w'igihugu, aho ijambo ryiwe rizosamirana mu Kibanza gitukura kandi rikurikiranwe cane kugira abantu bamenye ibigiye gukurikira
 Umukuru w'igihugu c'Uburusia akunze gukoresha kenshi aka karyo kugira ngo ashikirize ubutumwa bwerekana integuro ziwe
 Ibirori vy'uyu Musi w'Intsinzi vyarahimbazwa rimwe rimwe ku ntwaro y'Abasoviyeti, bikaba vyagiye kunagurwa na Perezida Boris Yeltsin  mw'ihimbazwa ry'isabukuru y'imyaka 50 mu 1995, ariko Perezida Vladimir Putin ni we yabigize ibirori ngarukamwaka kuva mu 2008, hakerekanwa ibikoresho vya gisirikare
 Umusi w'Intsinzi uri mu bintu  ndangagihugu vy'Uburusiya, aho ibitabo bikoreshwa mu mashure n'ibitabo vya kahise vyibanda cane ku Burusiya nk'igihugu gitabara Ubulaya mu gihe c'intambara
 "No mu bihe bisanzwe, ni akaryo gakomeye ko kwerekana inguvu z'Uburusiya, ubushobozi bwa Putin n'ibindi vyose ahagarariye", nk'uko bivugwa na Ammon Cheskin wo kw'ishure kaminuza ya Glasgow
 "Uno mwaka rero bizoba bikomeye"
 Amakuru avuga ko ashobora kuzotangaza ko ahagaritse intambara yarabeshujwe, co kimwe n'ayavuga ko azotangaza intambara yeruye canke guhamagarira Abarusiya b'abagabo kuja mu gisirikare
 Umushikiranganji ajejwe imigenderanire Sergei Lavrov avuga ko igisirikare c'Uburusiya "kitopfa kugira ico gihinduye mu bikorwa"  vyaco kubera itariki runaka gusa
 Ntihabuze ikizoshikirizwa ariko atari uguhamagarira uwubishoboye wese kuja ku rugamba, ariko bizohakwa gusa n'ivyo, kubera ibintu vyinshi Uburusiya bumaze gutakaza muri iyo ntambara, ariko ivyo navyo bishobora gutuma umukuru w'igihugu atakaza icizere c'abanyagihugu
 Inyuma y'aho Uburusiya bwigaruriye Crimée/Crimea mu 2014, Vladimir Putin yamye ahimbaza Umusi w'Intsinzi n'ijambo ashikiriza ku Kibanza Gitukura ku bijanye no gutsinda ubutegetsi bw'agahotoro (fascism), imbere yo kwurira indege imushikana ku kivuko ca Sevastopol ku Nyanja Yirabura (Mer Noire/ Black Sea) guhimbaza intsinzi yiwe nshasha imbere y'ibihumbi n'ibihumbi vy'abarorerezi
 "Uno mwaka intego nyamukuru kwari ugutangaza intsinzi yari yitezwe mu kwa kabiri", niko Ernest Wyciszkiewicz  wo ku kigo Centre for Polish-Russian Dialogue and Understanding avuga
 Ati: "Bariko bategura ibintu bikomeye bazokwerekana ku wa mbere: ni ngombwa ko Abarusiya babona ko igikorwa kidasanzwe ca gisirikare bagize imisi babwirwa cashitse ku kintu kiboneka"
 Haguhimbaza isenyuka rya reta ya Ukraine, Kremlin izotegerezwa kwibanda kw'ifatwa rya Mariupol
 Iki gisagara gishobora gusigara ari umunyota, ariko Uburusiya bwamye buvuga ko bushaka gukuraho "intwaro y'Abanazi hamwe no gusambura igisirikare" ca Ukraine, kandi bushobora gutangaza ko bwatsinze ingabo za Ukraine zirwanira i Azov muri ico gisagara bwamye bwerekana ko ari ic'Abanazi
 Iki coba ari ikintu cumvikana ku munsi w'Intambara ya kabiri yisi yose
 "Mu bisagara vy'Uburusiya no ku migwa mikuru y'uburere, turabona ibimenyetso vy'umusi w'Intsinzi", niko Olga Irisova ari mu batanguje ikigo c'abahinga, Riddle Russia, avuga
 "Mu bisanzwe ibi bimenyetso bisanzwe vyerekana 9 Rusama ariko uno mwaka vyerekana 1945/2022, rero bariko bagerageza gushira mu banyagihugu iciyumviro c'uko bongeye gutsinda Abanazi"
 I Mariupol ubwayo nta defire y'umusi w'Intsinzi izoberayo kubera bibaza ko umutekano ushobora kuba atari mwiza
 Umutegetsi w'ako karere yashizweho n'Uburusiya Denis Pushilin avuga ko iyo defire izotegerezwa kurindirizwa gushika aho Mariupol izokwegukira ico yise Repubulika ya Donetsk (République populaire de Donetsk/Donetsk People's Republic)
 Hazoba ibirori bitazwi neza, n'aho bishobora kwerekanwa cane mu binyamakuru vy'Uburusiya
 Mu bikorwa vyo kwitegurira ibirobi vyo ku wa 9 Rusama, ico gisagara caragendewe n'umunyamakuru ashikiriza amakuru ya Kremlin Vladimir Solovyov hamwe n'intumwa za Kremlin zirongowe n'icegera c'umukuru w'ibiro vy'umukuru w'igihugu, Sergei Kiryenko
 Idefire y'Umusi w'Intsinzi ibera ku Kibanza Gitukura ni kandi ukwerekana isura nziza, hamwe kandi n'ibikoresho vya gisirikare
 Ni akaryo ka Kremlin ko gushira ahabona ibirwanisho bishasha
 Mu birori nk'ibi vyo mu 2015, ikimodoka ntamenwa Armata T-14 nico cerekanywe gusumba, ariko rero cagizweko amakenga kubona kitakoreshejwe mu ntambara ya Ukraine, kubera kitari bwategurwe neza kugira ngo gishobore gukoreshwa ku rugamba
 Ukraine ivuga ko imaze gusambura ibimodoka ntamenwa birenga 1000 vy'Uburusiya ku rugamba
 Hazoba hari ibirwanisho bike n'ingabo nkeya ugereranije no mu 2021
 Ariko hazoshobora kuba hari ingabo 10
000 n'ubwoko bw'ibikoresho vya gisirikare 129, nk'uko biri mu mwihwezo w'umunyamakuru wa BBC mu rurimi rw'ikirusiya
 Indege zizokwerekanwa ku bwinshi nk'uko vyahora, indege na kajugujugu 77, ingabo zirwanira mu kirere zikaba zimaze igihe zikora imyimenyerezo ku Kibanza Gitukura mu kimenyetso c'urudome Z - ikimenyetso kiranga ingabo zateye Ukraine
 Ariko nta bategetsi mvamakungu bazobaho muri uno mwaka, Kremlin ikavuga ko ari ukubera y'uko isabukuru igira 77 atari ibirori bikomeye ubwavyo
 Ariko ubutumwa hafi bwose bujanye n'Umusi w'Intsinzi buhabwa Abarusiya, nk'uko Olga Irisova abivuga
 Mu gukoresha amajambo ashingiye ku ba Nazi bo mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose, Kremlin iratahurwa cane kubera Abarusiya hafi bose bafise ababo baguye muri iyo ntambara canke bayirwanye
 Mu gihe ibirori bizoba mu gihugu cose mu Burusiya, iyi tariki ya 9 Rusama igenda itakaza agaciro mu bihugu bibanyi
 Ukraine yarahaburiye abantu batari bake, amatohoza aheruka akerekana ko uwo musi woba ukwiye uwo kwibukirako abaguye muri iyo ntambara hakuba umusi w'intsinzi
 Ku mwaka ugira gatatu yikurikiranya, Kazakhstan yarahagaritse idefire yayo ya gisirikare, mu gihe Lettonie/Latvia nayo yawufashe nk'umusi wo kwibuka - abaguye mu ntambara y'Uburusiya muri Ukraine

Perezida Joe Biden yagenye  Karine Jean-Pierre nk'umuvugizi mushasha wiwe mukuru  - bukaba ari bwo bwa mbere umwirabure, canke uwemanga ko ari mu bahuza ibitsina babisangiye (gay), agenwa muri ico kibanza
 Madamu Jean-Pierre Karine w'imyaka 44 yahora ari icegera c'umunyamabanga mukuru ajejwe kumenyesha amakuru kuva Biden atowe
 Agiye kuzosubirira Jen Psaki w'imyaka 43 muri ico kibanza kuva mu mpera z'indwi iza
 Abanyamabanga bajejwe kumenyesha amakuru bama bategura ibiganiro n'abanyamakuru ba Maison Blanche/White House umusi ku musi, ibi bikavuga ko iki gishobora kuba ikibanza gikomeye cane
 Madamu Psaki agiye gukora mu kinyamakuru MSNBC cegamiye uruhande rw'abashaka ko ibintu bihinduka (left-wing)
 Aciye kuri Twitter, yavuze ko uwugiye kumusubirira ari "umugore adasanzwe" kandi "agendera ibanga"
 Ati: "Ndindiranye igishika cinshi kumubona ingene akora neza kuko azananye ubuhinga, ubwira n'ubuntu bimuranga"
 Umupfasoni Jean-Pierre, imbere y'aha akaba yari umuhinga kuri MSNBC, aje afise uburambe bw'imyaka irenga 20 muri poritike y'aba Démocrates
 Uyu mupfasoni yavukiye mw'izinga ry'Ubufaransa rya Martinique muri Caraïbes hanyuma agakurira i Queens muri New York, yari umwe mu bategetsi ba poritike ku ntwaro ya Obama
 Mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu yo mu 2016,  yari umuvugizi mukuru wa MoveOn, ishirahamwe rikomeye riharanira ukwishira n'ukwizana
 Imbere y'uko yinjira mu murwi w'abajejwe kumenyesha amakuru muri Maison Blanche, yari umukuru w'ibiro vya Kamala Harris amaze kugenwa na Biden kugira yiyamamarize hamwe na we nk'icegera c'umukuru w'igihugu
 Igenwa ry'umupfasoni Jean-Pierre ribaye imbere y'amatora akomeye y'abashingamateka yo mu kwa cumi na rimwe azokwerekana ingene ikiringo kizoba gisigaye c'ubutegetsi bwa Biden kizoba kimeze

