Igihe naja Calais ku kazi ka Focus on Africa, sinibaza ko nosanga hariho casino (inzu bakiniramwo akamari)
 Iki gisagara co ku kivuko mu Bufaransa ntikizwi cane mu gukina akamari, ariko iyo casino iri hanze y'ihoteri nashikiyemwo yibutsa ko twagira tubonane n'abantu bakora vyanke bikunde, bizigiye ko bashobora gutombora amafaranga menshi - yobashikana mu Bwongereza
 Twamaranye akanya n'abafata ko ayo makambi ari ho imuhira iwabo
 Ku bisanzwe izo kambi zugawe icese mu 2016 - ariko amashirahamwe afasha avuga ko abantu bashika 1
500 bakiba muri imwe twari turamutse tugendera
 Hafi ya bose, umwe umwe wese afise ingene ategura gushika mu Bwongereza
  Irfan* nawe kuri ico ntatandukanye n'abandi - ariko hari ico yisangije
 Bitandukanye n'abandi bose, uwu muhungu w'umuyabaga yasa n'uko ari wenyene - gushika haje uwufasha gusobonura ivyo avuga (interpreter)
 Yavuye iwabo  mu mezi 18 aheze, mu rugendo rubangamye rwamucishije mu bihugu bitandukanye birimwo Libya, Ubutariyano, n'Ububirigi
 Uwo muhungu w'imyaka 16 avuga ko yavuye iwabo kugira aje kurondera kazoza keza gusumba
 "Muri Eritrea nta mwidegemvyo uhari kandi ku  myaka 18 uca utegerezwa kuja mu gisirikare", niko avuga
 Twashatse kumenya niba amasezerano hagati ya reta z'Ubwomgereza n'Urwanda  azogira ingaruka ku migambi yiwe
 Abashasha bajabuka English Channel (Manche) bashobora  kuja mu bazorungikwa kurondera ubuhungiro no kwubaka ubuzima bwabo mu Rwanda, muri Afrika
 Reta y'Ubwongereza ivuga ko uwo mugambi mushasha uzoca intege abantu bafata bene izo ngendo - ariko abagwanya uwo mugambi bavuga ko abantu nka Irfan bavuga ko bahitamwo gukoresha ubwato canke amakamyo kugira bashike mu Bwongereza kuko badashobora gusaba ubuhungiro batarashika ku butaka bw'Ubwongereza
 Irfan yambariye ko ataravugana n'umuryango wiwe haraheze amezi abiri
 "Umuryango wanje ntuzi iyo ndi, ntiturashobora kuvugana
" Uwasigura ivyo avuga, umwe mu bakozi b'ishirahamwe ry'abagiraneza afasha abo barondera ubuhungiro bari Calais,  atanguye kunanirwa kwihangana igihe ariko asobonura  amajambo ya Irfan
 Aciye yunamika umutwe, biranka ko avuga aca atangura kurira
 Nca ndaraba ko ameze neza, angirira ikimenyetso c'umutwe ko ameze neza
 Aca arihagararako
 Turakomeza kuyaga
 "Ndakumbuye abo tuvukana
 Gushika ubu maze umwaka n'igice ngenda, sinzi uko bamerewe," aho uwusobanura amajambo yari ashoboye gusubiranwo ivyo Irfan yari yavuze imbere
 Nca ndamubaza nti: "Bizogenda gute bagufashe bakakurungika mu Rwanda?" "Ubwongereza ni gihugu kigendera ku mategeko", uwo ni Irfan yishuye
 "Reta y'Ubwongereza izondungika mu Rwanda? Hariya n'intwaro y'igitugu
" "Nibashimika, sinibaza ko nzoguma mu Rwanda
" U Rwanda rufatwa nk'igihugu kirimwo intwaro y'umukazo n'amashirahamwe atari make aharanira agateka ka zina muntu nka Human Rights Watch
 Paul Kagame, umukuru w'u Rwanda, ari ku butegetsi kuva mu 1994 kandi mu gihe ashimagizwa kuba yaratumye u Rwanda rugira amaragamo inyuma ya jenoside, yagirizwa kuba yashinze ubutegetsi bw'umugambwe umwe
 Irfan afise ishaka ryo kurondera ubuhungiro mu Bwongereza, kuko yibaza ko aho azofatwa neza kurusha mu Bufaransa
 Calais yabaye nk'ikimenyetso c'akaga  k'ikibazo c'abarondera ubuhungiro i Buraya
 Abantu ngaha bagerageza gushika mu Bwongereza mu ngendo zisa no kwiheba mu bwato canke mu kwinyegeza mu ma kamyo canke itereni
 Mu kwezi kw'indwi mu 2016 imbere y'uko ubutegetsi bw'Ubufaransa busambura iyo kambi ya Calais, urusansuma rw'ishirahamwe ry'abagiraneza Help Refugees rwagereranya ko abantu barenga 7
000 baba aho hantu
